{
  "9Xm4ieF32qQ": {
    "video_id": "9Xm4ieF32qQ",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.13.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171114",
    "duration": 544,
    "view_count": 330,
    "description": "November 13, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-FRATERNITY HAZING DEATH CHARGES\n-DEADLY IRAN-IRAQ EARTHQUAKE\n-COSTA RICA EARTHQUAKE \n-A LOOK INSIDE TEXAS CHURCH MEMORIAL\n-ROY MOORE'S WIFE SPEAKS OUT\n-FIRST HIJAB WEARING BARBIE\n-VOLCANO LAVA MELTS GOPRO\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CN",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.024, \"end\": 17.924, \"text\": \"In February of this year\"}, {\"start\": 18.0, \"end\": 23.0, \"text\": \"Penn State University student Timothy\"}, {\"start\": 23.0, \"end\": 28.0, \"text\": \"Piazza died after his first night of pledging\"}, {\"start\": 28.0, \"end\": 33.0, \"text\": \"Beta Theta Pi fraternity.\"}, {\"start\": 34.0, \"end\": 39.0, \"text\": \"Now 26 members of the fraternity have been charged with his death.\"}, {\"start\": 39.0, \"end\": 44.0, \"text\": \"The charges were filed after the discovery of new video from the\"}, {\"start\": 44.0, \"end\": 49.0, \"text\": \"night of Piazza's death. The district attorney says\"}, {\"start\": 50.0, \"end\": 54.0, \"text\": \"the surveillance video shows fraternity brothers\"}, {\"start\": 54.0, \"end\": 58.0, \"text\": \"giving Piazza at least 18 drinks\"}, {\"start\": 59.0, \"end\": 66.0, \"text\": \"in an 82 minute period. The video\"}, {\"start\": 67.0, \"end\": 72.0, \"text\": \"also showed him falling down a flight of stairs.\"}, {\"start\": 73.0, \"end\": 78.0, \"text\": \"An autopsy revealed his\"}, {\"start\": 78.0, \"end\": 82.0, \"text\": \"blood alcohol content was between\"}, {\"start\": 83.0, \"end\": 88.0, \"text\": \".26 and .36 the night that he died.\"}, {\"start\": 89.0, \"end\": 94.0, \"text\": \"One fraternity member tried to erase the video\"}, {\"start\": 95.0, \"end\": 99.0, \"text\": \"but police recovered it. He will\"}, {\"start\": 99.0, \"end\": 104.0, \"text\": \"be charged with tampering with evidence.\"}, {\"start\": 104.0, \"end\": 107.0, \"text\": \"The other fraternity members will be charged with\"}, {\"start\": 108.0, \"end\": 112.0, \"text\": \"involuntary manslaughter, assault,\"}, {\"start\": 113.0, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"hazing and furnishing alcohol to minors.\"}, {\"start\": 122.0, \"end\": 127.0, \"text\": \"At least 452 people were killed and thousands\"}, {\"start\": 128.0, \"end\": 133.0, \"text\": \"injured after a powerful earthquake struck near the border\"}, {\"start\": 133.0, \"end\": 140.0, \"text\": \"of Iran and Iraq late Sunday night.\"}, {\"start\": 140.0, \"end\": 144.0, \"text\": \"Most of the victims were in the\"}, {\"start\": 144.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"Kerman Shah province of western Iran.\"}, {\"start\": 149.0, \"end\": 154.0, \"text\": \"The 7.3 magnitude quake also\"}, {\"start\": 154.0, \"end\": 159.0, \"text\": \"claimed lives in northern Iraq where at least seven people died.\"}, {\"start\": 159.0, \"end\": 164.0, \"text\": \"According to the U.S. Geological survey\"}, {\"start\": 164.0, \"end\": 171.0, \"text\": \"tremors were felt throughout the Middle East.\"}, {\"start\": 171.0, \"end\": 175.0, \"text\": \"This earthquake is the deadliest\"}, {\"start\": 175.0, \"end\": 183.0, \"text\": \"of the year, surpassing the one that hit Mexico City in September.\"}, {\"start\": 185.0, \"end\": 190.0, \"text\": \"There were actually two earthquakes last night.\"}, {\"start\": 191.0, \"end\": 193.0, \"text\": \"A 6.1 magnitude earthquake\"}, {\"start\": 194.0, \"end\": 199.0, \"text\": \"struck off the coast of Costa Rica on\"}, {\"start\": 199.0, \"end\": 204.0, \"text\": \"Sunday evening.\"}, {\"start\": 205.0, \"end\": 208.0, \"text\": \"Three people suffered fatal heart attacks coinciding with\"}, {\"start\": 208.0, \"end\": 213.0, \"text\": \"the time of the quake. At least one building had to be evacuated due to\"}, {\"start\": 214.0, \"end\": 218.0, \"text\": \"damage and there were some reports of walls collapsing\"}, {\"start\": 219.0, \"end\": 224.0, \"text\": \"and objects falling. But there\"}, {\"start\": 224.0, \"end\": 229.0, \"text\": \"were no reports of any further injuries.\"}, {\"start\": 229.0, \"end\": 234.0, \"text\": \"Costa Rica's hospitals are functioning properly and\"}, {\"start\": 234.0, \"end\": 238.0, \"text\": \"minor power outages were restored quickly.\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 245.0, \"text\": \"Take a look at this.\"}, {\"start\": 245.001, \"end\": 247.901, \"text\": \"This is what the inside of First\"}, {\"start\": 248.0, \"end\": 252.0, \"text\": \"Baptist Church in Sutherland Springs\"}, {\"start\": 253.0, \"end\": 257.0, \"text\": \"Texas looks like.\"}, {\"start\": 258.0, \"end\": 262.0, \"text\": \"Volunteers worked day and night to turn the\"}, {\"start\": 262.0, \"end\": 267.0, \"text\": \"deadly crime scene into a memorial to honor\"}, {\"start\": 267.0, \"end\": 273.0, \"text\": \"the 26 people who died there two Sundays ago.\"}, {\"start\": 273.0, \"end\": 277.0, \"text\": \"The carpet has been taken out,\"}, {\"start\": 278.0, \"end\": 282.0, \"text\": \"pews have been removed and the entire sanctuary\"}, {\"start\": 282.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"is painted white from the floor to the ceiling.\"}, {\"start\": 287.0, \"end\": 291.0, \"text\": \"There are 26 chairs placed in the exact spot\"}, {\"start\": 292.0, \"end\": 297.0, \"text\": \"where someone's body was found with their name written in gold\"}, {\"start\": 297.0, \"end\": 304.0, \"text\": \"on the back and a red rose on the seat.\"}, {\"start\": 304.001, \"end\": 306.901, \"text\": \"There is one pink rose for the\"}, {\"start\": 307.0, \"end\": 312.0, \"text\": \"unborn baby that was killed in the shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 312.0, \"end\": 317.0, \"text\": \"Family and friends of the victims say the memorial is an important part of the\"}, {\"start\": 317.0, \"end\": 324.0, \"text\": \"healing process and will help them find closure.\"}, {\"start\": 325.0, \"end\": 328.0, \"text\": \"The wife of Alabama Senate candidate\"}, {\"start\": 328.0, \"end\": 334.0, \"text\": \"Roy Moore is defending her husband.\"}, {\"start\": 335.0, \"end\": 338.0, \"text\": \"Moore is accused of pursuing relationships with\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 343.0, \"text\": \"teenagers when he was in his 30s including a sexual encounter with a\"}, {\"start\": 343.0, \"end\": 347.0, \"text\": \"14 year old girl.\"}, {\"start\": 347.024, \"end\": 353.924, \"text\": \"Kayla Moore blames the Democratic party and\"}, {\"start\": 354.0, \"end\": 358.0, \"text\": \"other powerful people in Washington, D.C. for trying to sabotage her husband's\"}, {\"start\": 359.0, \"end\": 364.0, \"text\": \"campaign. She posted on Facebook that the entire scandal is a witch hunt and that\"}, {\"start\": 364.0, \"end\": 372.0, \"text\": \"they are threatening to sue the Washington Post for\"}, {\"start\": 372.0, \"end\": 378.0, \"text\": \"publishing the article. She also said prayers are appreciated.\"}, {\"start\": 380.001, \"end\": 382.999, \"text\": \"Last year fencer\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 388.0, \"text\": \"Ibtihaj Muhammad\"}, {\"start\": 388.0, \"end\": 393.0, \"text\": \"became the first American olympian to\"}, {\"start\": 393.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"compete while wearing a hijab. Now toy maker Mattel\"}, {\"start\": 398.0, \"end\": 403.0, \"text\": \"has unveiled a new Barbie created\"}, {\"start\": 403.0, \"end\": 410.0, \"text\": \"in her honor.\"}, {\"start\": 411.001, \"end\": 414.001, \"text\": \"The doll is the newest\"}, {\"start\": 414.1, \"end\": 418.0, \"text\": \"inductee into the Barbie \\\"Shero\\\" series. According to Mattel\"}, {\"start\": 418.0, \"end\": 422.0, \"text\": \"the \\\"Sheros\\\" program was created to honor women\"}, {\"start\": 423.0, \"end\": 427.0, \"text\": \"who break barriers.\"}, {\"start\": 427.0, \"end\": 432.0, \"text\": \"The new doll will be available starting in 2018.\"}, {\"start\": 434.001, \"end\": 437.001, \"text\": \"Take a look at this.\"}, {\"start\": 437.002, \"end\": 441.902, \"text\": \"This is amazing, up-close video of a tour\"}, {\"start\": 442.0, \"end\": 446.0, \"text\": \"guide's GoPro becoming engulfed in\"}, {\"start\": 446.024, \"end\": 451.024, \"text\": \"a lava flow in Hawaii.\"}, {\"start\": 451.025, \"end\": 454.025, \"text\": \"Eric Storm says\"}, {\"start\": 454.1, \"end\": 459.1, \"text\": \"it happened by accident while he was\"}, {\"start\": 460.0, \"end\": 464.0, \"text\": \"guiding a tour back in August 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 464.0, \"end\": 469.0, \"text\": \"Storm says he used a rock hammer to\"}, {\"start\": 469.0, \"end\": 474.0, \"text\": \"extract the camera after the lava began\"}, {\"start\": 474.0, \"end\": 479.0, \"text\": \"to cool and harden. He thought the camera\"}, {\"start\": 479.0, \"end\": 484.0, \"text\": \"had surely been destroyed but was\"}, {\"start\": 484.0, \"end\": 492.0, \"text\": \"amazed to see the blue wifi light still blinking.\"}, {\"start\": 493.0, \"end\": 500.0, \"text\": \"And as you can see the footage of the lava was all there.\"}, {\"start\": 500.001, \"end\": 503.001, \"text\": \"Some critics say the incident was staged\"}, {\"start\": 503.1, \"end\": 510.1, \"text\": \"and Storm left the camera there on purpose.\"}, {\"start\": 510.101, \"end\": 515.101, \"text\": \"But Storm says the video is real.\"}, {\"start\": 517.0, \"end\": 520.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 521.0, \"end\": 523.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1 News.\"}, {\"start\": 523.024, \"end\": 527.024, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 528.0, \"end\": 534.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "P7crM7PwnTk": {
    "video_id": "P7crM7PwnTk",
    "title": "Multiple fatalities in Miami bridge collapse (ASL - 3.15.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180316",
    "duration": 108,
    "view_count": 269,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.599, \"end\": 8.149, \"text\": \"Just after the lunch hour today a pedestrian bridge collapsed in Miami.\"}, {\"start\": 8.149, \"end\": 20.38, \"text\": \"The bridge was at Florida International University over SW 8th St. connecting the campus to the\"}, {\"start\": 20.38, \"end\": 22.22, \"text\": \"student housing area.\"}, {\"start\": 22.22, \"end\": 30.8, \"text\": \"911 calls started pouring in about 1:30 PM.\"}, {\"start\": 30.8, \"end\": 37.24, \"text\": \"Officials say 8 cars were crushed underneath the 950 ton bridge.\"}, {\"start\": 37.24, \"end\": 39.7, \"text\": \"Several people were transported to hospitals.\"}, {\"start\": 39.7, \"end\": 45.24, \"text\": \"At this time police have not released how many people were killed.\"}, {\"start\": 45.24, \"end\": 52.12, \"text\": \"Officials say a police officer who owns a business across the street from the bridge\"}, {\"start\": 52.12, \"end\": 55.2, \"text\": \"was first on the scene and helped victims until others arrived.\"}, {\"start\": 55.2, \"end\": 59.98, \"text\": \"Several law enforcement agencies are assisting in the search and rescue effort, including\"}, {\"start\": 59.98, \"end\": 61.3, \"text\": \"rescue dogs.\"}, {\"start\": 61.3, \"end\": 65.7, \"text\": \"They say their primary goal is looking for survivors.\"}, {\"start\": 65.7, \"end\": 70.42, \"text\": \"Police ordered helicopters hovering over the scene to move away from the scene so they\"}, {\"start\": 70.42, \"end\": 73.42, \"text\": \"could hear the voices of any survivors.\"}, {\"start\": 73.42, \"end\": 78.18, \"text\": \"The bridge was just installed Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 78.18, \"end\": 84.28, \"text\": \"At this point investigators aren't sure what caused the collapse.\"}, {\"start\": 84.28, \"end\": 89.46, \"text\": \"Officials are asking people who normally drive in the area to stay away so investigators\"}, {\"start\": 89.52, \"end\": 91.9, \"text\": \"can work.\"}, {\"start\": 91.9, \"end\": 96.36, \"text\": \"Police also gave out a phone number for \\\"family members only\\\" who may be concerned about their\"}, {\"start\": 96.36, \"end\": 97.74, \"text\": \"loved ones.\"}, {\"start\": 97.74, \"end\": 106.62, \"text\": \"The number is (305) 348-3481.\"}]"
  },
  "dcI96iQtgJg": {
    "video_id": "dcI96iQtgJg",
    "title": "Candace Jones shines at FSDB Homecoming (ASL - 10.25.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20181026",
    "duration": 222,
    "view_count": 466,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.74, \"end\": 11.28, \"text\": \"This past weekend Sign1News anchor Candace Jones headed back to her alma mater, Florida\"}, {\"start\": 11.28, \"end\": 18.78, \"text\": \"School for the Deaf and the Blind (FSDB).\"}, {\"start\": 18.78, \"end\": 26.44, \"text\": \"She was invited to be the grand marshal of the homecoming parade.\"}, {\"start\": 26.44, \"end\": 39.02, \"text\": \"But while she was there, she shared her life story and life lessons for hundreds of students\"}, {\"start\": 39.02, \"end\": 41.82, \"text\": \"and they hung on her every word.\"}, {\"start\": 49.3, \"end\": 52.06, \"text\": \"Big cheers went up at the Florida School for the Deaf and the Blind.\"}, {\"start\": 52.06, \"end\": 75.62, \"text\": \"FSDB alumni and Sign1News anchor Candace Jones was back and leading the homecoming celebration.\"}, {\"start\": 75.63, \"end\": 83.829, \"text\": \"This was a weekend of reflection for Candace.\"}, {\"start\": 83.829, \"end\": 90.45, \"text\": \"It felt like only yesterday she was a student herself, a young girl with dreams of one day\"}, {\"start\": 90.45, \"end\": 98.96, \"text\": \"being successful.\"}, {\"start\": 98.96, \"end\": 104.42, \"text\": \"And now she's back as a successful news anchor, speaking to hundreds of students eager to\"}, {\"start\": 104.42, \"end\": 106.82, \"text\": \"hear about her life's journey.\"}, {\"start\": 106.82, \"end\": 111.9, \"text\": \"You know that my memories here at FSDB are the best memories of my life.\"}, {\"start\": 111.9, \"end\": 118.82, \"text\": \"The friends, the teachers, the staff, some of my closest relationships all started here.\"}, {\"start\": 118.82, \"end\": 124.4, \"text\": \"When I graduated I remembered all the skills I learned in high school like reading, writing,\"}, {\"start\": 124.4, \"end\": 127.88, \"text\": \"signing, acting and sports.\"}, {\"start\": 127.88, \"end\": 133.76, \"text\": \"All of those life skills I learned here at FSDB. This is my home.\"}, {\"start\": 133.76, \"end\": 138.24, \"text\": \"When she finished her speech, Candace asked for volunteers from the audience.\"}, {\"start\": 138.24, \"end\": 141.44, \"text\": \"She wanted to give the students a little taste of what it's like to be a news anchor.\"}, {\"start\": 141.44, \"end\": 145.0, \"text\": \"The students were given a real-life news story and were asked to translate it as if it were\"}, {\"start\": 145.0, \"end\": 146.92, \"text\": \"a real broadcast.\"}, {\"start\": 146.92, \"end\": 151.04, \"text\": \"They only had 15 minutes to do it.\"}, {\"start\": 151.04, \"end\": 161.88, \"text\": \"The students rose to the challenge and did an amazing job as mock news anchors.\"}, {\"start\": 161.88, \"end\": 164.76, \"text\": \"Afterwards we got a chance to speak with one of Candace's former teachers, Deborah Penrose,\"}, {\"start\": 164.76, \"end\": 166.56, \"text\": \"who said she was not surprised Candace turned into an amazing woman because she was an amazing\"}, {\"start\": 166.56, \"end\": 167.92, \"text\": \"student.\"}, {\"start\": 167.92, \"end\": 169.92, \"text\": \"Oh yes definitely!\"}, {\"start\": 169.92, \"end\": 175.52, \"text\": \"And now she is inspiring other students who watch her as a Sign1News anchor.\"}, {\"start\": 175.52, \"end\": 177.48, \"text\": \"It encourages them to try to emulate her.\"}, {\"start\": 177.48, \"end\": 181.88, \"text\": \"The ripple effects are simply amazing.\"}, {\"start\": 181.88, \"end\": 183.52, \"text\": \"Oh how I enjoy that.\"}, {\"start\": 183.52, \"end\": 186.44, \"text\": \"They really love and look up to her and want to be like her.\"}, {\"start\": 186.44, \"end\": 190.44, \"text\": \"Candace had these parting words for the students at FSDB.\"}, {\"start\": 190.44, \"end\": 196.08, \"text\": \"I want to let the students know that no matter what your dreams and goals are, no matter\"}, {\"start\": 196.08, \"end\": 203.56, \"text\": \"the frustrations or obstacles that you will encounter sometimes, you have to consistently\"}, {\"start\": 203.56, \"end\": 205.8, \"text\": \"and passionately keep going after your dreams.\"}, {\"start\": 205.8, \"end\": 210.52, \"text\": \"Even if you veer off course, just get back on track and keep going until you reach your goals.\"}, {\"start\": 210.52, \"end\": 211.56, \"text\": \"That's the important thing.\"}, {\"start\": 211.56, \"end\": 218.12, \"text\": \"It's easier said than done but do all you can to keep going with all the passion you\"}, {\"start\": 218.12, \"end\": 219.64, \"text\": \"can muster.\"}, {\"start\": 219.64, \"end\": 222.0, \"text\": \"It will lead you to places you never thought you'd go.\"}]"
  },
  "uY583WM9yJw": {
    "video_id": "uY583WM9yJw",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.24.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171124",
    "duration": 429,
    "view_count": 170,
    "description": "November 24, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-MOSQUE ATTACK KILLS HUNDREDS\n-THOUSANDS GATHER FOR NEW ZIMBABWE PRESIDENT\n-ARGENTINE SUB MISSING, EXPLOSION HEARD NEARBY\n-FRANKEN ISSUES NEW APOLOGY\n-TRUMP GOLFS WITH TIGER WOODS\n-TODAY IS BLACK FRIDAY!\n-BLACK FRIDAY VS CYBER MONDAY\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.88, \"end\": 10.26, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.26, \"end\": 13.98, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall and here are your top  stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.64, \"end\": 20.02, \"text\": \"A mosque was attacked today in Egypt's North Sinai province.\"}, {\"start\": 20.02, \"end\": 25.38, \"text\": \"After two explosions, gunmen, who were waiting outside the mosque,\"}, {\"start\": 25.38, \"end\": 31.56, \"text\": \"opened fire as worshipers fled Friday prayers.\"}, {\"start\": 31.56, \"end\": 36.5, \"text\": \"At least 235 people were killed. One hundred and 25 people were injured --\"}, {\"start\": 36.5, \"end\": 42.02, \"text\": \"making it one of the deadliest attacks every carried out against civilians in the province.\"}, {\"start\": 42.06, \"end\": 46.82, \"text\": \"The blast caused considerable damage to the mosque.\"}, {\"start\": 46.88, \"end\": 53.84, \"text\": \"An Egyptian health ministry spokesman described the incident as a terrorist attack.\"}, {\"start\": 53.92, \"end\": 58.92, \"text\": \"Egyptian president Abdel Fatah el-Sisi\"}, {\"start\": 58.92, \"end\": 64.54, \"text\": \"is meeting with a security committee to discuss repercussions of the attack.\"}, {\"start\": 64.54, \"end\": 69.98, \"text\": \"The president has also declared three days of national mourning.\"}, {\"start\": 71.16, \"end\": 77.22, \"text\": \"For the first time in 37 years, Zimbabwe has a new leader.\"}, {\"start\": 77.22, \"end\": 82.72, \"text\": \"Tens of thousands of cheering and dancing people\"}, {\"start\": 82.72, \"end\": 86.12, \"text\": \"filled the National Sports Stadium in Harare\"}, {\"start\": 86.12, \"end\": 90.72, \"text\": \"to watch Emmerson Mnangagwa being sworn in\"}, {\"start\": 90.72, \"end\": 93.42, \"text\": \"as the country's new interim president.\"}, {\"start\": 93.44, \"end\": 98.1, \"text\": \"Elections for a permanent successor are expected next year.\"}, {\"start\": 98.14, \"end\": 101.074, \"text\": \"The former president Robert Mugabe\"}, {\"start\": 101.08, \"end\": 107.92, \"text\": \"was forced to resign on Tuesday after a military coup.\"}, {\"start\": 107.92, \"end\": 113.54, \"text\": \"Critics say Mugabe stayed in office far too long\"}, {\"start\": 113.58, \"end\": 116.86, \"text\": \"and had become a corrupt dictator who oppressed\"}, {\"start\": 116.86, \"end\": 118.96, \"text\": \"people and ruined the economy.\"}, {\"start\": 118.96, \"end\": 121.38, \"text\": \"Despite his corrupt reign,\"}, {\"start\": 121.38, \"end\": 125.3, \"text\": \"military officials say he and his wife\"}, {\"start\": 125.34, \"end\": 130.22, \"text\": \"have been granted immunity,\"}, {\"start\": 130.22, \"end\": 134.04, \"text\": \"which will allow them to remain in the country\"}, {\"start\": 134.04, \"end\": 137.34, \"text\": \"and gives them a guarantee of safety.\"}, {\"start\": 138.62, \"end\": 143.28, \"text\": \"More than a week has passed since an Argentine Navy submarine\"}, {\"start\": 143.28, \"end\": 147.66, \"text\": \"vanished in the Atlantic Ocean.\"}, {\"start\": 147.68, \"end\": 150.7, \"text\": \"Now hopes of a rescue are fading.\"}, {\"start\": 150.72, \"end\": 155.9, \"text\": \"But now government officials say an unexplained explosion\"}, {\"start\": 155.9, \"end\": 159.74, \"text\": \"on Thursday was detected near the last confirmed location of the sub.\"}, {\"start\": 159.84, \"end\": 162.34, \"text\": \"Government officials gave an update to the families after the explosion took place.\"}, {\"start\": 162.34, \"end\": 167.34, \"text\": \"They want to assure them that the explosion wasn't evidence of any sort of an attack on the sub.\"}, {\"start\": 167.34, \"end\": 173.12, \"text\": \"Teams from 12 nations have been involved in the hunt for sub.\"}, {\"start\": 173.12, \"end\": 178.34, \"text\": \"It was supposed to have docked Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 178.34, \"end\": 182.7, \"text\": \"Experts say that in the ocean's depths,\"}, {\"start\": 182.7, \"end\": 187.3, \"text\": \"the sub would only have 7 to 10 days worth of oxygen on board.\"}, {\"start\": 187.3, \"end\": 191.6, \"text\": \"But the crew might have bought itself more time\"}, {\"start\": 191.62, \"end\": 197.96, \"text\": \"by raising a tube to the surface and refreshing the air inside the vessel.\"}, {\"start\": 199.62, \"end\": 205.82, \"text\": \"Democratic Senator Al Franken is making a new apology\"}, {\"start\": 205.82, \"end\": 210.5, \"text\": \"amid growing allegations of sexual harassment.\"}, {\"start\": 210.54, \"end\": 213.54, \"text\": \"In a statement released Thursday Franken said he feels\"}, {\"start\": 213.54, \"end\": 218.22, \"text\": \"terrible that he made some women feel badly.\"}, {\"start\": 218.22, \"end\": 223.04, \"text\": \"Franken also writes that he crossed the line in some encounters with women.\"}, {\"start\": 223.04, \"end\": 228.76, \"text\": \"The new apology comes days after a woman accused Franken\"}, {\"start\": 228.78, \"end\": 235.52, \"text\": \"of groping her during a photo at the Minnesota State fair\"}, {\"start\": 235.52, \"end\": 239.86, \"text\": \"in 2010 -- a year after he joined the Senate.\"}, {\"start\": 239.86, \"end\": 244.1, \"text\": \"Last week a Los Angeles radio personality accused\"}, {\"start\": 244.1, \"end\": 250.7, \"text\": \"Franken of forcibly kissing and groping her more than a decade ago.\"}, {\"start\": 250.7, \"end\": 257.98, \"text\": \"Franken now faces a potential investigation by the Senate ethics committee.\"}, {\"start\": 259.64, \"end\": 266.34, \"text\": \"President Trump worked off his Thanksgiving dinner on the golf course.\"}, {\"start\": 266.34, \"end\": 272.22, \"text\": \"He sent out this tweet morning.\"}, {\"start\": 272.22, \"end\": 278.92, \"text\": \"It says after turkey I will be heading over to Trump National Golf Club\"}, {\"start\": 278.92, \"end\": 288.02, \"text\": \"to play with Tiger Woods and Dustin Johnson,\"}, {\"start\": 288.02, \"end\": 292.16, \"text\": \"then back to Mar-a-Lago for talks on bringing\"}, {\"start\": 292.16, \"end\": 297.48, \"text\": \"even more jobs and companies back to the USA.\"}, {\"start\": 298.72, \"end\": 302.82, \"text\": \"Retailers are still banking on a big bang to kick off the\"}, {\"start\": 302.82, \"end\": 305.76, \"text\": \"first major weekend of the crucial holiday shopping season --\"}, {\"start\": 305.76, \"end\": 308.22, \"text\": \"both in the store and online.\"}, {\"start\": 308.22, \"end\": 312.94, \"text\": \"Black Friday  has lost some of the hype in recent years\"}, {\"start\": 313.0, \"end\": 318.26, \"text\": \"but it is still a big day for shoppers and for retailers.\"}, {\"start\": 318.28, \"end\": 321.3, \"text\": \"It's a big opportunity for retailers to gauge how\"}, {\"start\": 321.3, \"end\": 327.1, \"text\": \"an estimated 115 million consumers feel about holiday shopping.\"}, {\"start\": 327.1, \"end\": 333.04, \"text\": \"Low unemployment and a higher stock market\"}, {\"start\": 333.14, \"end\": 336.72, \"text\": \"seem to point to holiday cheer in the malls while shopping.\"}, {\"start\": 336.72, \"end\": 342.64, \"text\": \"The National Retail Federation expects overall holiday\"}, {\"start\": 342.64, \"end\": 346.4, \"text\": \"sales to increase as much as four percent over last year\"}, {\"start\": 346.4, \"end\": 350.7, \"text\": \"up to $682 billion.\"}, {\"start\": 350.76, \"end\": 353.04, \"text\": \"While some shoppers want nothing to do with\"}, {\"start\": 353.06, \"end\": 355.78, \"text\": \"crowded malls and parking hassles,\"}, {\"start\": 355.78, \"end\": 357.66, \"text\": \"others say they love it.\"}, {\"start\": 357.66, \"end\": 361.24, \"text\": \"It's part of their holiday tradition.\"}, {\"start\": 362.32, \"end\": 369.02, \"text\": \"Retailers may be hoping for big sales on Thanksgiving and Black Friday\"}, {\"start\": 369.02, \"end\": 373.86, \"text\": \"but Cyber Monday maybe even bigger.\"}, {\"start\": 373.96, \"end\": 378.84, \"text\": \"Adobe Analytics is forecasting this coming Monday\"}, {\"start\": 378.84, \"end\": 383.26, \"text\": \"as the largest online shopping day in U.S. history.\"}, {\"start\": 383.26, \"end\": 390.42, \"text\": \"Americans are expected to spend $6.6 billion online\"}, {\"start\": 390.42, \"end\": 396.4, \"text\": \"compared to $5 billion online for Black Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 396.4, \"end\": 400.34, \"text\": \"Cyber Monday began in 2005\"}, {\"start\": 400.34, \"end\": 404.68, \"text\": \"as a way to promote the relatively new concept of online retail.\"}, {\"start\": 406.1, \"end\": 408.1, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 408.1, \"end\": 409.44, \"text\": \"I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 409.44, \"end\": 411.32, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 411.36, \"end\": 415.1, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 415.1, \"end\": 421.06, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "kMz7cPfI3NM": {
    "video_id": "kMz7cPfI3NM",
    "title": "Sign1News fan video of the day (ASL - 2.7.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180208",
    "duration": 178,
    "view_count": 261,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.82, \"end\": 17.3, \"text\": \"Sign1News fan Nikole Kolenda sent us an adorable video of her son Damon practicing ASL with her.\"}, {\"start\": 17.32, \"end\": 25.82, \"text\": \"Damon is hearing but his father Dillon is a CODA.\"}, {\"start\": 25.82, \"end\": 34.62, \"text\": \"Dillon's parents and several other members of the family are deaf so Damon is learning\"}, {\"start\": 34.62, \"end\": 37.02, \"text\": \"ASL so he can communicate with the extended family.\"}, {\"start\": 37.02, \"end\": 45.34, \"text\": \"Nikole says Damon's signs are not perfect but he sure is expressive!\"}, {\"start\": 45.38, \"end\": 46.64, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 47.4, \"end\": 49.2, \"text\": \"Apple.\"}, {\"start\": 51.32, \"end\": 54.24, \"text\": \"Hurt.\"}, {\"start\": 54.86, \"end\": 61.06, \"text\": \"Airplane. (Nikole: Airplane?) Airplane.\"}, {\"start\": 63.52, \"end\": 65.72, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's food?) Food.\"}, {\"start\": 67.24, \"end\": 70.04, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's drink?) Eat.\"}, {\"start\": 70.04, \"end\": 73.2, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's drink?) Drink.\"}, {\"start\": 74.56, \"end\": 76.64, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's hot?) Hot. Hot.\"}, {\"start\": 77.2, \"end\": 80.0, \"text\": \"Horsey. (Nikole: Horsey. Yeah.)\"}, {\"start\": 80.64, \"end\": 82.64, \"text\": \"Mamma may I have a drink of water?\"}, {\"start\": 82.64, \"end\": 85.92, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's water?) Water. Water.\"}, {\"start\": 86.24, \"end\": 92.48, \"text\": \"(Nikole: Water. (laughter)) What is the sign for cold?)\"}, {\"start\": 92.48, \"end\": 93.92, \"text\": \"Cold!\"}, {\"start\": 95.28, \"end\": 98.72, \"text\": \"(Nikole: Forgot. (laughter))\"}, {\"start\": 99.36, \"end\": 100.56, \"text\": \"Daddy.\"}, {\"start\": 100.56, \"end\": 103.4, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's mommy?) Mommy.\"}, {\"start\": 103.4, \"end\": 104.66, \"text\": \"(Nikole: Good job.)\"}, {\"start\": 104.66, \"end\": 106.88, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's thank you?) Thank you.\"}, {\"start\": 106.88, \"end\": 110.12, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What is please?) Please.\"}, {\"start\": 113.32, \"end\": 115.52, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What is peach?) Peach.\"}, {\"start\": 116.48, \"end\": 118.58, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's flower?) Flower.\"}, {\"start\": 118.58, \"end\": 119.94, \"text\": \"(Nikole: (laughter) Good job.)\"}, {\"start\": 120.88, \"end\": 125.76, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What is more?) More. More.\"}, {\"start\": 126.48, \"end\": 128.86, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's deer?) Deer.\"}, {\"start\": 131.0, \"end\": 133.08, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's mad? I'm mad!)\"}, {\"start\": 133.14, \"end\": 135.72, \"text\": \"Yeah!!! (laughter)\"}, {\"start\": 135.76, \"end\": 139.88, \"text\": \"Mad! Mad! Mad!\"}, {\"start\": 140.68, \"end\": 149.24, \"text\": \"Nikole thank you for sending us this adorable video and for encouraging Damon to learn ASL.\"}, {\"start\": 149.38, \"end\": 154.4, \"text\": \"I was born hearing and became deaf at three years old.\"}, {\"start\": 154.52, \"end\": 156.36, \"text\": \"I learned ASL in school.\"}, {\"start\": 156.44, \"end\": 160.12, \"text\": \"My teachers would give me papers with pictures that demonstrated how to sign words.\"}, {\"start\": 160.12, \"end\": 165.32, \"text\": \"I would take those vocabulary words home to show my family so we could learn ASL at the\"}, {\"start\": 165.36, \"end\": 167.04, \"text\": \"same time.\"}, {\"start\": 167.04, \"end\": 173.4, \"text\": \"It is important that children are bilingual, learning both English and ASL.\"}, {\"start\": 173.4, \"end\": 176.86, \"text\": \"Nikole great job!  Keep up the good work.\"}]"
  },
  "DUPvK46M_rs": {
    "video_id": "DUPvK46M_rs",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.11.2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171212",
    "duration": 557,
    "view_count": 457,
    "description": "December 11, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-NYC PORT AUTHORITY EXPLOSION SUSPECT\n-SENATORS CALL FOR TRUMP RESIGNATION\n-CALIFORNIA WILDFIRE BATTLE CONTINUES\n-MILITARY MUST ACCEPT TRANSGENDER RECRUITS\n-BOY'S EMOTIONAL PLEA ON BULLYING GOES VIRAL\n-PANDA FLIPS OUT OVER SNOW\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE Our talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GAL",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.08, \"end\": 11.02, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.06, \"end\": 12.18, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 12.26, \"end\": 14.42, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.8, \"end\": 24.92, \"text\": \"Police arrested this man -- 27-year-old Akayed Ullah -- in connection to the attempted terrorist\"}, {\"start\": 24.98, \"end\": 31.28, \"text\": \"attack Monday morning in New York City.\"}, {\"start\": 31.36, \"end\": 39.82, \"text\": \"The police commissioner says Ullah wore an improvised low-tech explosive device attached\"}, {\"start\": 39.92, \"end\": 48.0, \"text\": \"to his body --  which he intentionally detonated at the\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 56.24, \"text\": \"Port Authority bus terminal near Times Square.\"}, {\"start\": 56.36, \"end\": 63.32, \"text\": \"The detonation was caught on security cameras.\"}, {\"start\": 63.36, \"end\": 72.82, \"text\": \"Ullah was treated for lacerations and burns to his hands and abdomen.\"}, {\"start\": 72.84, \"end\": 76.48, \"text\": \"Three other people were injured as well.\"}, {\"start\": 76.54, \"end\": 84.2, \"text\": \"Investigators say Ullah told them recent Israeli actions in Gaza are\"}, {\"start\": 84.22, \"end\": 93.16, \"text\": \"the reason he carried out the attack.\"}, {\"start\": 93.2, \"end\": 102.0, \"text\": \"Police not sure if Ullah is linked to any terror organizations.\"}, {\"start\": 103.52, \"end\": 112.08, \"text\": \"A group of women who say President Trump was inappropriate with them detail their stories\"}, {\"start\": 112.14, \"end\": 115.46, \"text\": \"at a news conference Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 115.48, \"end\": 120.54, \"text\": \"It was organized by a production company that made a film about them.\"}, {\"start\": 120.56, \"end\": 129.6, \"text\": \"Accusations of sexual misconduct by Trump first surfaced when he was running for president.\"}, {\"start\": 129.7, \"end\": 132.92, \"text\": \"At least 13 women have come forward.\"}, {\"start\": 133.0, \"end\": 140.48, \"text\": \"Their stories included details of Trump forcibly kissing them and inappropriate touching.\"}, {\"start\": 140.48, \"end\": 152.44, \"text\": \"Today New York Senator Kirsten Gillibrand says Trump should resign\"}, {\"start\": 152.44, \"end\": 156.46, \"text\": \"in light of these sexual assault claims against him.\"}, {\"start\": 156.46, \"end\": 162.62, \"text\": \"She says the accusations are numerous and credible.\"}, {\"start\": 162.82, \"end\": 170.84, \"text\": \"Gillibrand is the third Democratic Senator to call for Trump's resignation.\"}, {\"start\": 170.88, \"end\": 181.16, \"text\": \"Cory Booker of New Jersey and Jeff Merkley of Oregon have\"}, {\"start\": 181.22, \"end\": 185.38, \"text\": \"also said the president should step down.\"}, {\"start\": 185.46, \"end\": 190.32, \"text\": \"Trump denies all of the allegations against him.\"}, {\"start\": 190.36, \"end\": 197.8, \"text\": \"During his 2016 campaign, he promised to sue his accusers.\"}, {\"start\": 197.86, \"end\": 201.0, \"text\": \"He has never filed a lawsuit against them.\"}, {\"start\": 202.22, \"end\": 208.48, \"text\": \"Wildfires continue to burn in Southern California\"}, {\"start\": 208.54, \"end\": 216.88, \"text\": \"and officials fear it could be days before weather conditions improve.\"}, {\"start\": 216.96, \"end\": 227.8, \"text\": \"California officials warn that the massive Thomas fire is still advancing and nearby\"}, {\"start\": 227.8, \"end\": 235.32, \"text\": \"communities must be prepared for the worst.\"}, {\"start\": 235.32, \"end\": 245.52, \"text\": \"The Thomas fire is one of several wildfires burning North and South of Los Angeles\"}, {\"start\": 245.56, \"end\": 252.92, \"text\": \"fueled by strong winds, above-normal temperatures and low humidity.\"}, {\"start\": 253.06, \"end\": 258.96, \"text\": \"Unfortunately forecasters say these weather conditions are going to remain in place for\"}, {\"start\": 258.97, \"end\": 262.85, \"text\": \"the next few days.\"}, {\"start\": 262.85, \"end\": 271.6, \"text\": \"Hundreds of thousands of acres have been scorched and tens of thousands of residents have been\"}, {\"start\": 271.6, \"end\": 274.66, \"text\": \"forced from their homes.\"}, {\"start\": 275.36, \"end\": 283.02, \"text\": \"On Monday a federal judge declined the US government's request to put on hold in order\"}, {\"start\": 283.02, \"end\": 291.04, \"text\": \"allowing transgender individuals to join the military beginning in January.\"}, {\"start\": 291.04, \"end\": 299.74, \"text\": \"The decision means transgender people will be free to enlist in the new year.\"}, {\"start\": 299.74, \"end\": 306.89, \"text\": \"So far two federal judges have blocked key provisions of President Trump's prohibition\"}, {\"start\": 306.89, \"end\": 311.28, \"text\": \"on transgender individuals serving in the military.\"}, {\"start\": 311.34, \"end\": 318.6, \"text\": \"Trump announced the ban on Twitter in July,\"}, {\"start\": 318.6, \"end\": 323.44, \"text\": \"then made it official with a directive memo in August.\"}, {\"start\": 323.44, \"end\": 331.12, \"text\": \"After Monday's ruling the Pentagon said it has already followed a court ruling last week\"}, {\"start\": 331.18, \"end\": 344.08, \"text\": \"and is planning to prepare to access transgender persons as of January 1.\"}, {\"start\": 344.08, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"The White House press secretary said the Justice Department is reviewing its legal options.\"}, {\"start\": 354.96, \"end\": 363.34, \"text\": \"A desperate Tennessee mother recorded her son describing the bullying he endures every\"}, {\"start\": 363.34, \"end\": 368.52, \"text\": \"day -- and posted the video on Facebook.\"}, {\"start\": 368.52, \"end\": 377.42, \"text\": \"The boy's name is Keaton and his story struck a chord with millions of people who watched.\"}, {\"start\": 377.5, \"end\": 378.64, \"text\": \"Here it is. Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 378.72, \"end\": 381.88, \"text\": \"Just out of curiosity why do they bully?\"}, {\"start\": 381.96, \"end\": 383.66, \"text\": \"What's the point of it?\"}, {\"start\": 383.72, \"end\": 390.3, \"text\": \"Why do you find joy in taking innocent people and finding ways to be mean to them?\"}, {\"start\": 390.36, \"end\": 392.52, \"text\": \"It's not okay.\"}, {\"start\": 392.52, \"end\": 394.56, \"text\": \"(Mother: What do they say to you?)\"}, {\"start\": 394.64, \"end\": 399.2, \"text\": \"They make fun of my nose, they call me ugly, they say I have no friends.\"}, {\"start\": 399.52, \"end\": 402.08, \"text\": \"(Mother: What did they do to you at lunch?)\"}, {\"start\": 402.24, \"end\": 407.04, \"text\": \"Pour milk on me and put their hands down my clothes (inaudible)\"}, {\"start\": 407.44, \"end\": 411.28, \"text\": \"(Mother: Is it just you or is it other kids that feel that way?)\"}, {\"start\": 411.6, \"end\": 414.48, \"text\": \"They say it's other kids too.\"}, {\"start\": 414.64, \"end\": 416.64, \"text\": \"(Mother: How does that make you feel?)\"}, {\"start\": 417.04, \"end\": 420.72, \"text\": \"I don't like that they do it to me and for sure don't like that they do it to other people\"}, {\"start\": 421.04, \"end\": 424.24, \"text\": \"because it's not okay.\"}, {\"start\": 424.48, \"end\": 428.0, \"text\": \"People that are different don't need to be criticized about it.\"}, {\"start\": 428.32, \"end\": 433.6, \"text\": \"It's not their fault.\"}, {\"start\": 434.24, \"end\": 441.12, \"text\": \"But if you are made fun of, just don't let it bother you.\"}, {\"start\": 441.44, \"end\": 443.84, \"text\": \"Stay strong I guess.\"}, {\"start\": 444.48, \"end\": 452.0, \"text\": \"It's hard but it will probably get better one day.\"}, {\"start\": 452.8, \"end\": 464.8, \"text\": \"Actor Chris Evans, who portrays Capt. America in the movies, tweeted a message to Keaton\"}, {\"start\": 465.28, \"end\": 472.16, \"text\": \"and invited him to the premier of the next Avengers movie.\"}, {\"start\": 472.64, \"end\": 487.04, \"text\": \"University of Tennessee quarterback Jarrett Guarantano visited Keaton in person on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 487.04, \"end\": 495.36, \"text\": \"He says Keaton is now the little brother he has always wanted.\"}, {\"start\": 496.9, \"end\": 498.98, \"text\": \"Check out this video.\"}, {\"start\": 499.1, \"end\": 502.76, \"text\": \"It's from the National Zoo in Washington D.C.\"}, {\"start\": 502.76, \"end\": 510.22, \"text\": \"It shows panda Mei Xiang going bananas over the snow.\"}, {\"start\": 510.22, \"end\": 518.26, \"text\": \"Cameras caught her rolling and somersaulting around in snow-cover leaves and grass Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 518.26, \"end\": 527.12, \"text\": \"According to the National Zoo, giant pandas are native to the cold climate\"}, {\"start\": 527.12, \"end\": 530.56, \"text\": \"and are more active in wintertime.\"}, {\"start\": 532.72, \"end\": 534.64, \"text\": \"And those your top stories today.\"}, {\"start\": 534.96, \"end\": 536.24, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 536.48, \"end\": 538.72, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 538.88, \"end\": 543.44, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 543.6, \"end\": 549.12, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "8Z9yl0lQdCo": {
    "video_id": "8Z9yl0lQdCo",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.21.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171122",
    "duration": 638,
    "view_count": 454,
    "description": "November 21, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nSign1News delivers news for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-CBS NEWS FIRES CHARLIE ROSE\n-WHITE HOUSE ASKS FOR FULL TRAVEL BAN\n-SEMINOLE HEIGHTS REWARD INCREASES TO $110K\n-ADDITIONAL REMAINS OF SGT. JOHNSON FOUND IN NIGER\n-CROWDS CELEBRATE MUGABE RESIGNATION\n-WHITEFISH LEAVING PUERTO RICO, WANTS $83M\n-IKEA RECALL\n-4 WAYS TO AVOID GERMS WHILE TRAV",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 13.0, \"end\": 17.0, \"text\": \"And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.0, \"end\": 24.0, \"text\": \"Charlie Rose's CBS News career is over. The network\"}, {\"start\": 24.0, \"end\": 28.0, \"text\": \"fired him on Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 29.0, \"end\": 34.0, \"text\": \"PBS also announced it will no longer distribute his nightly\"}, {\"start\": 35.0, \"end\": 39.0, \"text\": \"talk show. Eight women have come forward accusing the anchor\"}, {\"start\": 39.0, \"end\": 44.0, \"text\": \"of sexual harassment. Rose was a co-host of 60 Minutes,\"}, {\"start\": 44.0, \"end\": 49.0, \"text\": \"CBS This Morning and the host of his\"}, {\"start\": 49.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"own interview show on PBS.\"}, {\"start\": 54.0, \"end\": 59.0, \"text\": \"CBS says the decision followed the revelation of\"}, {\"start\": 59.0, \"end\": 63.0, \"text\": \"extremely disturbing and intolerable behavior. The accusations against him\"}, {\"start\": 63.0, \"end\": 67.0, \"text\": \"include inappropriate phone calls, unwanted\"}, {\"start\": 67.0, \"end\": 72.0, \"text\": \"sexual advances and groping.\"}, {\"start\": 72.1, \"end\": 78.1, \"text\": \"The Washington Post broke the news, publishing the women stories.\"}, {\"start\": 79.0, \"end\": 84.0, \"text\": \"Rose apologized saying he behaved insensitively. He felt he it was mutual behavior\"}, {\"start\": 84.0, \"end\": 86.0, \"text\": \"but now he knows that's not the case.\"}, {\"start\": 87.0, \"end\": 92.0, \"text\": \"The Trump administration has asked the U.S. Supreme\"}, {\"start\": 93.0, \"end\": 98.0, \"text\": \"Court to allow the latest version of its\"}, {\"start\": 98.0, \"end\": 102.0, \"text\": \"controversial travel ban to\"}, {\"start\": 103.0, \"end\": 108.0, \"text\": \"go fully into effect. A district court in\"}, {\"start\": 108.0, \"end\": 112.0, \"text\": \"Hawaii blocked the latest version last month\"}, {\"start\": 113.0, \"end\": 118.0, \"text\": \"but a federal appeals court partially lifted the block earlier\"}, {\"start\": 118.0, \"end\": 123.0, \"text\": \"this month. The court ruled that the ban can go into\"}, {\"start\": 123.0, \"end\": 128.0, \"text\": \"effect except for foreign nationals who have bona\"}, {\"start\": 128.0, \"end\": 133.0, \"text\": \"fide relationships with people or entities in\"}, {\"start\": 133.0, \"end\": 138.0, \"text\": \"the United States. The new travel\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 142.0, \"text\": \"ban places various levels of restrictions on foreign\"}, {\"start\": 142.0, \"end\": 146.0, \"text\": \"nationals from eight countries.\"}, {\"start\": 147.0, \"end\": 151.0, \"text\": \"Those nations are Chad, Iran\"}, {\"start\": 152.0, \"end\": 155.0, \"text\": \"Libya, North Korea,\"}, {\"start\": 157.0, \"end\": 162.0, \"text\": \"Syria, Venezuela\"}, {\"start\": 163.0, \"end\": 167.0, \"text\": \"Somalia and Yemen.\"}, {\"start\": 168.0, \"end\": 173.0, \"text\": \"Since early October four people have been shot and killed\"}, {\"start\": 174.0, \"end\": 182.0, \"text\": \"in the Seminole Heights Florida neighborhood.\"}, {\"start\": 183.0, \"end\": 190.0, \"text\": \"Police have released this video of the suspect.\"}, {\"start\": 191.0, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"The latest killing occurred in the early morning hours on November\"}, {\"start\": 196.0, \"end\": 200.0, \"text\": \"14th. The victims were separated by age,\"}, {\"start\": 201.0, \"end\": 206.0, \"text\": \"race and occupation and each was killed,\"}, {\"start\": 206.0, \"end\": 210.0, \"text\": \"but not robbed, while walking alone at night\"}, {\"start\": 211.0, \"end\": 215.0, \"text\": \"within a half mile area.\"}, {\"start\": 216.0, \"end\": 221.0, \"text\": \"Investigators believe the killer lives in the neighborhood and\"}, {\"start\": 221.0, \"end\": 226.0, \"text\": \"that most likely they have spoken with him before.\"}, {\"start\": 227.0, \"end\": 231.0, \"text\": \"Now the reward for information leading to an arrest and\"}, {\"start\": 231.0, \"end\": 235.0, \"text\": \"conviction for the murders has risen\"}, {\"start\": 236.0, \"end\": 239.0, \"text\": \"to $110 thousand dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 240.0, \"end\": 245.0, \"text\": \"Additional remains have been discovered of Sergeant\"}, {\"start\": 246.0, \"end\": 253.0, \"text\": \"La David Johnson in Niger.\"}, {\"start\": 253.0, \"end\": 258.0, \"text\": \"Johnson was one of four Americans killed in an\"}, {\"start\": 258.0, \"end\": 263.0, \"text\": \"October ambush by ISIS.\"}, {\"start\": 263.0, \"end\": 268.0, \"text\": \"According to a U.S. official the remains were recovered by\"}, {\"start\": 268.0, \"end\": 273.0, \"text\": \"the military and FBI team that traveled to the area. The remains were discovered\"}, {\"start\": 273.0, \"end\": 277.0, \"text\": \"at the site where his body was recovered nearly a mile away from the site of the\"}, {\"start\": 277.0, \"end\": 282.0, \"text\": \"ambush. Johnson's family was notified on Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 282.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"It's unclear if the additional remains will provide any clues about\"}, {\"start\": 287.0, \"end\": 288.0, \"text\": \"Johnson's death.\"}, {\"start\": 289.024, \"end\": 291.024, \"text\": \"Thousands of people danced and cheered\"}, {\"start\": 292.0, \"end\": 297.0, \"text\": \"in the streets of Zimbabwe last night after hearing the news\"}, {\"start\": 297.0, \"end\": 302.0, \"text\": \"that the country's president Robert Mugabe\"}, {\"start\": 303.0, \"end\": 308.0, \"text\": \"had resigned. He ruled the country for 37 years\"}, {\"start\": 308.0, \"end\": 313.0, \"text\": \"and was the the only leader the nation has known since 1980.\"}, {\"start\": 313.0, \"end\": 318.0, \"text\": \"Parliament had already begun proceedings to impeach him\"}, {\"start\": 318.0, \"end\": 323.0, \"text\": \"and the military had already\"}, {\"start\": 323.0, \"end\": 328.0, \"text\": \"seized control. Under his reign he waged a campaign of\"}, {\"start\": 328.0, \"end\": 332.0, \"text\": \"oppression and pushed the country into poverty.\"}, {\"start\": 332.0, \"end\": 337.0, \"text\": \"Yet over the decades Mugabe and his wife lived\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 340.0, \"text\": \"lavish lifestyles.\"}, {\"start\": 340.024, \"end\": 344.024, \"text\": \"There is no immediate announcement of who would take over for Mugabe.\"}, {\"start\": 345.0, \"end\": 351.0, \"text\": \"Two months have passed since Hurricane Maria tore through Puerto Rico.\"}, {\"start\": 351.0, \"end\": 356.0, \"text\": \"Power generation on the island is still only about 50 percent.\"}, {\"start\": 356.0, \"end\": 361.0, \"text\": \"Whitefish Energy, the company that was hired\"}, {\"start\": 362.0, \"end\": 366.0, \"text\": \"to restore energy, has halted its efforts.\"}, {\"start\": 366.0, \"end\": 371.0, \"text\": \"The company says Puerto Rico's electric utility owes\"}, {\"start\": 371.0, \"end\": 376.0, \"text\": \"it $83 million dollars. The contract was originally for\"}, {\"start\": 376.0, \"end\": 382.0, \"text\": \"$300 million dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 386.0, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico's governor moved to void the contract after\"}, {\"start\": 386.0, \"end\": 391.0, \"text\": \"realizing Whitefish only had\"}, {\"start\": 391.024, \"end\": 395.024, \"text\": \"two full time employees.\"}, {\"start\": 395.1, \"end\": 401.1, \"text\": \"State and federal authorities are investigating the contract.\"}, {\"start\": 403.0, \"end\": 406.0, \"text\": \"Ikea is issuing a recall on Malm\"}, {\"start\": 407.0, \"end\": 412.0, \"text\": \"dressers and chests.\"}, {\"start\": 412.0, \"end\": 418.0, \"text\": \"The Consumer Product Safety\"}, {\"start\": 418.0, \"end\": 422.0, \"text\": \"Commission says\"}, {\"start\": 422.0, \"end\": 427.0, \"text\": \"eight children have reportedly died\"}, {\"start\": 427.0, \"end\": 431.0, \"text\": \"after furniture from the line fell on top of them.\"}, {\"start\": 431.0, \"end\": 437.0, \"text\": \"The most recent toddler death happened this past May in California.\"}, {\"start\": 437.0, \"end\": 441.0, \"text\": \"The chest and the drawers in question are unstable if not\"}, {\"start\": 441.0, \"end\": 445.0, \"text\": \"properly anchored to the wall.\"}, {\"start\": 445.0, \"end\": 448.0, \"text\": \"Ikea is offering full refunds for the dresser\"}, {\"start\": 448.0, \"end\": 454.0, \"text\": \"if it was manufactured from 2002 to 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 455.0, \"end\": 458.0, \"text\": \"Customers can also request\"}, {\"start\": 458.024, \"end\": 463.024, \"text\": \"a free wall anchoring kit.\"}, {\"start\": 465.048, \"end\": 467.948, \"text\": \"An estimated 28.5 million people will\"}, {\"start\": 468.0, \"end\": 475.0, \"text\": \"fly on U.S. airlines during the Thanksgiving holiday period.\"}, {\"start\": 475.0, \"end\": 481.0, \"text\": \"If you happen to be one of those travelers\"}, {\"start\": 481.024, \"end\": 485.024, \"text\": \"here are four helpful tips to help you avoid germs.\"}, {\"start\": 486.048, \"end\": 488.048, \"text\": \"Sit toward the front of the plane. Air ventilation\"}, {\"start\": 488.1, \"end\": 492.1, \"text\": \"systems on most commercial aircraft provide better air flow in the air front.\"}, {\"start\": 493.0, \"end\": 498.0, \"text\": \"Don't drink coffee or tea on an airplane. The Environmental\"}, {\"start\": 499.0, \"end\": 504.0, \"text\": \"Protection Agency\"}, {\"start\": 504.0, \"end\": 511.0, \"text\": \"says airplane water tanks aren't always clean.\"}, {\"start\": 511.0, \"end\": 514.0, \"text\": \"Sanitize your hands after leaving an airplane bathroom.\"}, {\"start\": 514.0, \"end\": 520.0, \"text\": \"An airplane toilet is\"}, {\"start\": 521.0, \"end\": 523.0, \"text\": \"probably one of the most germ-infested places.\"}, {\"start\": 523.024, \"end\": 525.024, \"text\": \"And finally wash or sanitize\"}, {\"start\": 526.0, \"end\": 534.0, \"text\": \"your hands after getting off an escalator and using an ATM.\"}, {\"start\": 536.0, \"end\": 540.0, \"text\": \"Police officers in Saltillo Mississippi\"}, {\"start\": 540.0, \"end\": 544.0, \"text\": \"are stopping motorists to\"}, {\"start\": 545.0, \"end\": 550.0, \"text\": \"hand out turkeys, not tickets.\"}, {\"start\": 550.0, \"end\": 555.0, \"text\": \"It's an effort to give back to the community during the holidays.\"}, {\"start\": 555.0, \"end\": 559.0, \"text\": \"Local businesses collected food and monetary donations\"}, {\"start\": 559.0, \"end\": 564.0, \"text\": \"to support the initiative. It is being called\"}, {\"start\": 564.0, \"end\": 570.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Giving 2017.\\\" Officers are hoping it will become an annual tradition.\"}, {\"start\": 572.0, \"end\": 579.0, \"text\": \"Gulf Shores Alabama police posted this cute\"}, {\"start\": 580.0, \"end\": 585.0, \"text\": \"video of officers and a K9 named Nitro\"}, {\"start\": 585.0, \"end\": 589.0, \"text\": \"doing pushups. The department said\"}, {\"start\": 590.0, \"end\": 594.0, \"text\": \"they were warming up and ready to apprehend any bad guys\"}, {\"start\": 595.0, \"end\": 600.0, \"text\": \"that break the law. The post has been viewed\"}, {\"start\": 600.0, \"end\": 608.0, \"text\": \"forty-seven thousand times and shared eleven hundred times on Facebook.\"}, {\"start\": 611.0, \"end\": 613.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 613.0, \"end\": 617.0, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 618.0, \"end\": 622.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 622.0, \"end\": 629.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "e2rNsEjzerw": {
    "video_id": "e2rNsEjzerw",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.25.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180226",
    "duration": 332,
    "view_count": 1044,
    "description": "2.25.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Severe storms across Midwest, South\n-Stoneman Douglas High School hosts open house\n-Mexican President cancels WH trip after call with Trump\n-Michelle Obama to release memoir in November \n-\"Black Panther\" dominates weekend box office\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.18, \"end\": 8.4, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.4, \"end\": 10.44, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.44, \"end\": 11.98, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.98, \"end\": 14.86, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.24, \"end\": 22.12, \"text\": \"According to the National Weather Service, several people in Kentucky were killed due\"}, {\"start\": 22.12, \"end\": 23.28, \"text\": \"to severe storms.\"}, {\"start\": 23.28, \"end\": 29.2, \"text\": \"The storm brought relentless rain, fierce winds and lots of damage.\"}, {\"start\": 29.2, \"end\": 35.88, \"text\": \"Most of the damage happened late Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 35.98, \"end\": 41.92, \"text\": \"Residents they when they looked outside and saw trees bowing they knew they had to go\"}, {\"start\": 41.92, \"end\": 45.06, \"text\": \"seek shelter.\"}, {\"start\": 45.06, \"end\": 50.08, \"text\": \"Parts of the state also dealt with massive flooding.\"}, {\"start\": 50.08, \"end\": 58.12, \"text\": \"And in some areas of Tennessee the storm ripped through home after home, destroy nearly everything\"}, {\"start\": 58.12, \"end\": 60.4, \"text\": \"in sight.\"}, {\"start\": 60.4, \"end\": 67.26, \"text\": \"In Ohio heavy rain led to widespread flooding.\"}, {\"start\": 67.26, \"end\": 73.32, \"text\": \"Even parts of Arkansas witnessed the devastation.\"}, {\"start\": 73.32, \"end\": 77.12, \"text\": \"At least one storm-related death has been confirmed there.\"}, {\"start\": 81.36, \"end\": 92.9, \"text\": \"An open house was held at Stoneman Douglas high school for survivors and their parents today.\"}, {\"start\": 93.04, \"end\": 101.22, \"text\": \"This is the first time students and parents have been inside the school since the shooting\"}, {\"start\": 101.22, \"end\": 102.24, \"text\": \"last week that claimed 17 lives.\"}, {\"start\": 102.24, \"end\": 112.54, \"text\": \"The school was open for three hours to let students look at any schedule changes and\"}, {\"start\": 112.54, \"end\": 115.44, \"text\": \"to ask for anything they need.\"}, {\"start\": 115.46, \"end\": 119.6, \"text\": \"Counselors and therapy dogs were on campus as well.\"}, {\"start\": 119.6, \"end\": 125.799, \"text\": \"Students are scheduled to return to school on Wednesday for half-day sessions the rest\"}, {\"start\": 125.8, \"end\": 128.38, \"text\": \"of the week.\"}, {\"start\": 132.16, \"end\": 145.04, \"text\": \"Mexican president Enrique Pena Nieto canceled his official trip to Washington, DC after\"}, {\"start\": 145.04, \"end\": 149.74, \"text\": \"a tense phone call with President Trump on February 20th.\"}, {\"start\": 149.74, \"end\": 157.12, \"text\": \"According to the Washington Post, Pena Nieto reportedly called off the trip because Trump\"}, {\"start\": 157.12, \"end\": 164.4, \"text\": \"refused to publicly affirm Mexico's position on a border wall, specifically that Mexico\"}, {\"start\": 164.4, \"end\": 168.24, \"text\": \"not pay for it.\"}, {\"start\": 168.24, \"end\": 175.86, \"text\": \"A White House official did tell CNN that call between the two leaders was less hostile than\"}, {\"start\": 175.86, \"end\": 180.5, \"text\": \"the one that occurred a year ago.\"}, {\"start\": 184.44, \"end\": 193.42, \"text\": \"Former First Lady Michelle Obama is working on a memoir.\"}, {\"start\": 193.44, \"end\": 198.16, \"text\": \"It will be titled \\\"Becoming: The Memoir\\\" by Michelle Obama.\"}, {\"start\": 198.16, \"end\": 209.28, \"text\": \"It will be published by Penguin Random House and is scheduled for release on November 13th.\"}, {\"start\": 209.28, \"end\": 218.48, \"text\": \"The book will be published globally in 24 languages.\"}, {\"start\": 218.48, \"end\": 223.87, \"text\": \"An audio version of the book will also be released, voiced by the former First Lady\"}, {\"start\": 223.87, \"end\": 226.48, \"text\": \"herself.\"}, {\"start\": 226.48, \"end\": 228.68, \"text\": \"It will be her second book.\"}, {\"start\": 228.68, \"end\": 242.16, \"text\": \"In 2012, she published \\\"American Grown,\\\" which documents the White House kitchen garden and\"}, {\"start\": 242.16, \"end\": 246.08, \"text\": \"promotes healthy living.\"}, {\"start\": 246.08, \"end\": 252.12, \"text\": \"Former president Barack Obama is also penning his memoir.\"}, {\"start\": 252.12, \"end\": 256.94, \"text\": \"It will also be published by Penguin Random House and is expected to come out sometime\"}, {\"start\": 256.96, \"end\": 259.44, \"text\": \"this year.\"}, {\"start\": 265.52, \"end\": 273.2, \"text\": \"\\\"Black Panther\\\" is still dominating the box office for a second weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 273.2, \"end\": 277.04, \"text\": \"The blockbuster movie took in an estimated hundred $108 million this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 277.04, \"end\": 288.8, \"text\": \"It's the second highest second weekend for a film.\"}, {\"start\": 288.8, \"end\": 295.04, \"text\": \"Only \\\"Star Wars: The Force Awakens\\\" made more money during its second weekend of release.\"}, {\"start\": 295.04, \"end\": 302.96, \"text\": \"\\\"Black Panther\\\" has made more than $700 million globally.\"}, {\"start\": 307.28, \"end\": 309.92, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 309.92, \"end\": 311.24, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 311.24, \"end\": 313.28, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 313.28, \"end\": 317.84, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 317.84, \"end\": 324.24, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "guZ3CJdANAA": {
    "video_id": "guZ3CJdANAA",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.4.19 - News for the Deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20191205",
    "duration": 564,
    "view_count": 1871,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n\n- Video shows 4 teens escape detention center, 2 caught\n- Government launches HIV prevention program\n- FBI warning: Your smart tv may be spying on you\n- Starbucks adds new holiday drink to its menu\n- Apple announces 1st ever Apple Music Awards\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and info",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 11.72, \"end\": 13.5, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 13.5, \"end\": 16.3, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News Live.\"}, {\"start\": 16.3, \"end\": 17.38, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 17.38, \"end\": 20.72, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 26.36, \"end\": 37.08, \"text\": \"On Saturday night four teenagers escaped a Nashville, Tennessee detention center and\"}, {\"start\": 37.08, \"end\": 40.96, \"text\": \"on Tuesday night two of them were caught and arrested.\"}, {\"start\": 41.32, \"end\": 53.44, \"text\": \"The two suspects who were caught are 16-year-old Decorrius Wright and 15-year-old Calvin Howse.\"}, {\"start\": 53.52, \"end\": 62.0, \"text\": \"Police are still searching for the two other suspects, 17-year-old Brandon Caruthers and\"}, {\"start\": 62.0, \"end\": 65.72, \"text\": \"17-year-old Morris Marsh.\"}, {\"start\": 65.72, \"end\": 76.76, \"text\": \"Caruthers is being charged as an adult in an armed robbery case and is now among Tennessee's\"}, {\"start\": 76.76, \"end\": 86.36, \"text\": \"most wanted fugitives and Marsh is accused of murder.\"}, {\"start\": 86.56, \"end\": 91.6, \"text\": \"The teenagers escaped the Davidson County Juvenile Detention Center and it was captured\"}, {\"start\": 91.6, \"end\": 94.62, \"text\": \"on the center's surveillance video.\"}, {\"start\": 94.7, \"end\": 105.48, \"text\": \"The video shows the teens running down empty hallways before busting out of the facility.\"}, {\"start\": 105.48, \"end\": 112.17, \"text\": \"The four were able to escape after the person supervising them was called away to stop a\"}, {\"start\": 112.17, \"end\": 116.86, \"text\": \"fight elsewhere in the building.\"}, {\"start\": 116.86, \"end\": 125.82, \"text\": \"Police say the company that manages the center waited more than half an hour after the escape\"}, {\"start\": 125.82, \"end\": 127.94, \"text\": \"before notifying police.\"}, {\"start\": 127.94, \"end\": 132.84, \"text\": \"The private detention contractor that managed the facility fired three of its employees\"}, {\"start\": 132.84, \"end\": 135.92, \"text\": \"and suspended another in connection to the breakout.\"}, {\"start\": 135.92, \"end\": 143.88, \"text\": \"The Tennessee Bureau of Investigation is offering a 25-hundred dollar reward for information\"}, {\"start\": 143.88, \"end\": 147.6, \"text\": \"that results in Caruther's arrest.\"}, {\"start\": 149.88, \"end\": 157.44, \"text\": \"On Tuesday a national program to provide free preventative drugs to uninsured Americans\"}, {\"start\": 157.48, \"end\": 159.84, \"text\": \"at risk of HIV was announced.\"}, {\"start\": 159.84, \"end\": 171.6, \"text\": \"The program is called \\\"Ready, Set, PrEP.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 171.72, \"end\": 187.76, \"text\": \"To qualify, participants must test negative for HIV, have a valid prescription for the\"}, {\"start\": 187.76, \"end\": 195.72, \"text\": \"medication, and not have any prescription drug coverage.\"}, {\"start\": 195.72, \"end\": 205.0, \"text\": \"The drugs will be donated by Gilead Sciences, makers of Truvada and Descovy, the only two\"}, {\"start\": 205.0, \"end\": 219.76, \"text\": \"PrEP medications currently approved by the U.S. Food and Drug Administration.\"}, {\"start\": 219.76, \"end\": 226.0, \"text\": \"PrEP is a HIV prevention pill.\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 237.6, \"text\": \"The company will donate over two million bottles annually, enough to treat 200-thousand Americans,\"}, {\"start\": 237.76, \"end\": 240.16, \"text\": \"for next level 11 years.\"}, {\"start\": 240.16, \"end\": 256.32, \"text\": \"In President Trump's February State of the Union speech he set the goal to end the HIV epidemic.\"}, {\"start\": 256.32, \"end\": 263.6, \"text\": \"In May, he announced the agreement with Gilead.\"}, {\"start\": 265.76, \"end\": 273.84, \"text\": \"The TV you're looking at right now could be spying on you!\"}, {\"start\": 273.84, \"end\": 281.92, \"text\": \"On Black Friday and Cyber Monday smart TVs were a big hit.\"}, {\"start\": 281.92, \"end\": 290.88, \"text\": \"So the FBI is getting the word out that screens with advanced tech, like cameras and microphones,\"}, {\"start\": 290.88, \"end\": 301.92, \"text\": \"could be hacked by cyber criminals, who could potentially snoop or stalk you.\"}, {\"start\": 301.92, \"end\": 313.76, \"text\": \"To protect yourself, the FBI recommends changing the default password and to update the software.\"}, {\"start\": 313.76, \"end\": 321.6, \"text\": \"Also consider putting black tape over the camera hole or disabling the microphone.\"}, {\"start\": 324.08, \"end\": 331.76, \"text\": \"Yesterday (Tuesday) Starbucks launched a new holiday-themed drink.\"}, {\"start\": 332.0, \"end\": 339.52, \"text\": \"The coffee company is adding \\\"Irish Cream Cold Brew,\\\" which is coffee mixed with Irish\"}, {\"start\": 339.52, \"end\": 350.16, \"text\": \"cream syrup and topped with vanilla sweet cream foam and cocoa powder.\"}, {\"start\": 351.92, \"end\": 362.68, \"text\": \"The new item is the company's second holiday-themed iced drink to join its menu in the past three years.\"}, {\"start\": 362.68, \"end\": 372.68, \"text\": \"In 2016, it offered a limited-time drink called the \\\"Spiced Sweet Cream Cold Brew.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 372.68, \"end\": 379.32, \"text\": \"Starbucks says 'Irish Cream Cold Brew' will be available at stores across the U.S. but\"}, {\"start\": 379.4, \"end\": 381.68, \"text\": \"only for a limited time.\"}, {\"start\": 386.0, \"end\": 396.2, \"text\": \"Today (Wednesday) Apple will be celebrating its first ever Apple Music Awards.\"}, {\"start\": 396.2, \"end\": 404.52, \"text\": \"The event will take place at 6:30 p.m. Pacific Standard Time at the Steve Jobs Theater in\"}, {\"start\": 404.76, \"end\": 407.84, \"text\": \"California and will be live streamed.\"}, {\"start\": 408.68, \"end\": 415.84, \"text\": \"On Monday Apple announced the winners of their awards show.\"}, {\"start\": 415.84, \"end\": 428.68, \"text\": \"Artist Billie Eilish was honored with \\\"Global Artist of the Year\\\" and will be celebrating\"}, {\"start\": 428.7, \"end\": 435.0, \"text\": \"her award with a special performance.\"}, {\"start\": 435.0, \"end\": 452.16, \"text\": \"Other winners include singer and rapper Lizzo who was awarded \\\"Breakthrough Artist of the Year.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 452.56, \"end\": 466.68, \"text\": \"And Lil Nas X won \\\"Song of the Year\\\" for \\\"Old Town Road.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 468.88, \"end\": 476.12, \"text\": \"Each winner will receive this prize.\"}, {\"start\": 476.12, \"end\": 487.32, \"text\": \"Apple says the design is inspired by the same chips that power digital music devices.\"}, {\"start\": 491.76, \"end\": 494.78, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 495.0, \"end\": 496.6, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 496.6, \"end\": 500.52, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News Live.\"}, {\"start\": 500.52, \"end\": 509.76, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our app too.\"}, {\"start\": 511.8, \"end\": 514.54, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 514.54, \"end\": 515.86, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 515.86, \"end\": 518.16, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "AIiXQEiY_kM": {
    "video_id": "AIiXQEiY_kM",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.19.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180320",
    "duration": 605,
    "view_count": 1391,
    "description": "3.19.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-4th Austin, TX explosion\n-Trump’s opioid plan, death penalty for drug dealers\n-Cops catch Costco crooks red-handed!\n-Deputy get into scuffle with suspect on highway\n-“Avengers” sets sales record\n-Your comments: Sonic to sell pickle juice slushies\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign La",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.3, \"end\": 8.68, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.68, \"end\": 10.52, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.52, \"end\": 12.24, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.24, \"end\": 15.62, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.48, \"end\": 28.56, \"text\": \"There have now been four explosions in Austin, Texas in one month.\"}, {\"start\": 28.56, \"end\": 37.28, \"text\": \"Here is a map of the locations and victims in each explosion.\"}, {\"start\": 37.28, \"end\": 41.1, \"text\": \"The first explosion happened on March 2.\"}, {\"start\": 41.1, \"end\": 47.12, \"text\": \"Thirty-nine year-old Anthony House was killed.\"}, {\"start\": 47.12, \"end\": 56.54, \"text\": \"There were two explosions on March 12 just a few miles from each other.\"}, {\"start\": 56.54, \"end\": 64.88, \"text\": \"Seventeen year-old Draylen Mason was killed in one of the explosions and a 75 year old\"}, {\"start\": 64.88, \"end\": 68.06, \"text\": \"woman was critically injured in the second.\"}, {\"start\": 68.06, \"end\": 76.54, \"text\": \"In the first three explosions bombs were stuffed inside packages and left on residents' doorsteps.\"}, {\"start\": 76.54, \"end\": 84.78, \"text\": \"The fourth and latest device was left on the side of a residential road Sunday night.\"}, {\"start\": 84.78, \"end\": 88.84, \"text\": \"Two men in their 20s were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 88.84, \"end\": 96.72, \"text\": \"And unlike the previous victims, police say Sunday's victims are white.\"}, {\"start\": 96.76, \"end\": 107.06, \"text\": \"Despite those differences, Austin police say a serial bomber is on the loose.\"}, {\"start\": 107.08, \"end\": 117.52, \"text\": \"Austin's police chief said the latest device was triggered by a tripwire and shows a higher\"}, {\"start\": 117.52, \"end\": 121.52, \"text\": \"level of sophistication and a higher level of skill.\"}, {\"start\": 121.52, \"end\": 127.2, \"text\": \"Police are now reaching out to people who live in the area of the explosions, asking\"}, {\"start\": 127.2, \"end\": 131.64, \"text\": \"if they have video surveillance on their houses.\"}, {\"start\": 131.64, \"end\": 137.94, \"text\": \"They want to analyze the footage to see if they can identify suspicious people, vehicles\"}, {\"start\": 137.94, \"end\": 141.7, \"text\": \"or anything that may be tied to the investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 141.7, \"end\": 151.98, \"text\": \"Police are also asking the suspect or suspects responsible to contact them.\"}, {\"start\": 151.98, \"end\": 157.64, \"text\": \"They say innocent people are getting hurt and it needs to come to a stop.\"}, {\"start\": 162.1, \"end\": 169.84, \"text\": \"President Trump and First Lady Melania Trump left Washington DC headed to New Hampshire\"}, {\"start\": 169.86, \"end\": 172.06, \"text\": \"today.\"}, {\"start\": 172.06, \"end\": 183.52, \"text\": \"The president plans to roll out his plan to tackle the nationwide opioid epidemic.\"}, {\"start\": 183.52, \"end\": 199.36, \"text\": \"The plan involves prevention and education through a sizable advertising campaign, improving\"}, {\"start\": 199.36, \"end\": 211.34, \"text\": \"the ability to find treatment through the federal government and helping people impacted\"}, {\"start\": 211.34, \"end\": 216.86, \"text\": \"by the opioid epidemic find jobs while fighting addiction.\"}, {\"start\": 216.86, \"end\": 226.05, \"text\": \"The plan also includes the death penalty for high-volume drug dealers.\"}, {\"start\": 226.05, \"end\": 234.5, \"text\": \"Trump has been outspoken about including the death penalty in his plan but this is the\"}, {\"start\": 234.5, \"end\": 241.76, \"text\": \"first time it has been included in an official administration plan.\"}, {\"start\": 241.76, \"end\": 250.2, \"text\": \"Congress recently appropriated $6 billion to help curb the opioid epidemic.\"}, {\"start\": 250.2, \"end\": 257.7, \"text\": \"Trump's plan will address how the administration believes that money should be spent.\"}, {\"start\": 259.78, \"end\": 264.56, \"text\": \"A group of Seattle police officers caught a couple of thieves red-handed.\"}, {\"start\": 264.56, \"end\": 268.32, \"text\": \"And the whole thing was caught on camera.\"}, {\"start\": 268.32, \"end\": 276.66, \"text\": \"On March 14, officers responded to a call of a shop lifting in progress at Costco.\"}, {\"start\": 276.66, \"end\": 284.92, \"text\": \"Store security recognized the suspects from a past incident and tipped off the cops.\"}, {\"start\": 284.92, \"end\": 294.34, \"text\": \"Officers confronted the suspected getaway driver and waited outside a rear exit.\"}, {\"start\": 294.34, \"end\": 302.94, \"text\": \"Moments later two suspects burst through the door carrying stolen computers and vacuums.\"}, {\"start\": 302.96, \"end\": 304.4, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 319.58, \"end\": 325.2, \"text\": \"According to store security, the group was suspected in another Cosco robbery from the\"}, {\"start\": 325.28, \"end\": 327.42, \"text\": \"same day.\"}, {\"start\": 327.42, \"end\": 335.16, \"text\": \"The three suspects were booked on robbery and theft charges.\"}, {\"start\": 337.98, \"end\": 345.2, \"text\": \"A man is facing charges after he got into a scuffle with a Georgia deputy.\"}, {\"start\": 345.2, \"end\": 352.58, \"text\": \"The video we're about to show you shows the deputy trying to arrest a man during a traffic\"}, {\"start\": 352.58, \"end\": 355.06, \"text\": \"stop but he resists.\"}, {\"start\": 355.06, \"end\": 357.42, \"text\": \"The suspect and deputy began to struggle on the side of the road.\"}, {\"start\": 357.42, \"end\": 361.88, \"text\": \"The suspect is seen pushing the deputy down, jumping back in his car and driving away as\"}, {\"start\": 361.88, \"end\": 364.38, \"text\": \"the deputy tries to hang on to the vehicle.\"}, {\"start\": 364.48, \"end\": 366.56, \"text\": \"It was all caught on camera.\"}, {\"start\": 394.44, \"end\": 398.98, \"text\": \"According to the Sheriff's office, after the suspect drove away a passerby followed him\"}, {\"start\": 398.98, \"end\": 401.84, \"text\": \"until the deputy caught up.\"}, {\"start\": 401.84, \"end\": 408.72, \"text\": \"After a high-speed chase and several law enforcement cars damaged in the process, deputies were\"}, {\"start\": 408.72, \"end\": 411.84, \"text\": \"able to force the suspect off the road and arrest him.\"}, {\"start\": 411.84, \"end\": 416.36, \"text\": \"He faces assault and drug charges.\"}, {\"start\": 416.36, \"end\": 422.84, \"text\": \"The Sheriff's office says a large number of Xanax pills were found in the man's possession.\"}, {\"start\": 425.08, \"end\": 434.62, \"text\": \"\\\"Avengers: Infinity War\\\" is already a recordbreaker!\"}, {\"start\": 434.62, \"end\": 446.06, \"text\": \"The Marvel movie needed just six hours to break online ticket seller Fandangos record\"}, {\"start\": 446.06, \"end\": 455.48, \"text\": \"for fastest selling superhero movie in the first 24 hours of presales.\"}, {\"start\": 455.58, \"end\": 462.56, \"text\": \"And online ticket seller Atom Tickets reported that \\\"Avengers\\\" sold more tickets in its first\"}, {\"start\": 462.56, \"end\": 467.62, \"text\": \"presale day than \\\"Black Panther\\\" sold in its first month.\"}, {\"start\": 467.62, \"end\": 473.52, \"text\": \"\\\"Avengers: Infinity War\\\" opens April 27.\"}, {\"start\": 476.46, \"end\": 485.82, \"text\": \"Last night we told you about Sonic's plan to sell pickle juice slushies starting in June.\"}, {\"start\": 485.82, \"end\": 490.74, \"text\": \"We wanted to know if you like the idea or were totally disgusted by it.\"}, {\"start\": 490.74, \"end\": 493.46, \"text\": \"I personally love the idea!\"}, {\"start\": 493.48, \"end\": 498.58, \"text\": \"First of all, pickle juice itself is heavenly delicious.\"}, {\"start\": 498.58, \"end\": 508.0, \"text\": \"Also I drink it whenever I have muscle aches or cramps and it helps the pain go away.\"}, {\"start\": 508.0, \"end\": 519.0, \"text\": \"Patty Schultz posted this comment on our Facebook page: \\\"I don't think I like pickle juice but\"}, {\"start\": 519.0, \"end\": 524.0, \"text\": \"pregnant ladies will go for it for sure.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 524.0, \"end\": 531.48, \"text\": \"Juliann Blair doesn't think it will taste good.\"}, {\"start\": 531.48, \"end\": 538.58, \"text\": \"She said: \\\"Bitter and high sodium. Tsk.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 538.58, \"end\": 543.42, \"text\": \"Kibbie Parsons posted a video comment.\"}, {\"start\": 543.42, \"end\": 545.2, \"text\": \"Here's what she had to say:\"}, {\"start\": 545.2, \"end\": 548.24, \"text\": \"\\\"I love pickle juice.\"}, {\"start\": 548.24, \"end\": 549.3, \"text\": \"But on my food?\"}, {\"start\": 549.44, \"end\": 551.12, \"text\": \"Not really.\"}, {\"start\": 553.38, \"end\": 555.6, \"text\": \"But then again why not try it.\"}, {\"start\": 556.9, \"end\": 560.7, \"text\": \"It's something new and different and interesting to try.\"}, {\"start\": 563.2, \"end\": 566.14, \"text\": \"Thank you for sharing everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 566.14, \"end\": 573.74, \"text\": \"Okay listen -- when the drink comes out in June, I will try it myself and let you know if it's\"}, {\"start\": 573.74, \"end\": 577.18, \"text\": \"thumbs up or thumbs down.\"}, {\"start\": 580.68, \"end\": 582.92, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 582.92, \"end\": 584.66, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 584.7, \"end\": 587.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 587.0, \"end\": 591.46, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 591.46, \"end\": 597.74, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "tSCEj6AeUjM": {
    "video_id": "tSCEj6AeUjM",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.14.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180215",
    "duration": 455,
    "view_count": 1257,
    "description": "2.14.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Mass shooting at Florida high school\n-Trump lawyer paid porn star $130k out of pocket\n-Broadway actor busted in prostitution ring\n-Flu warning signs for kids\n-Home Depot hiring 80k seasonal employees\n-Obamas tweet Valentine's Day love messages to each other\n\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in Ame",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.94, \"end\": 8.36, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.36, \"end\": 11.64, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.64, \"end\": 13.16, \"text\": \"I’m Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.16, \"end\": 16.2, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.64, \"end\": 26.96, \"text\": \"Broward County police say a lone gunman opened fire at Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School today.\"}, {\"start\": 26.96, \"end\": 35.92, \"text\": \"Authorities say the shooting started just before 3 PM.\"}, {\"start\": 35.92, \"end\": 40.68, \"text\": \"Dozens of law-enforcement agencies -- police, fire, ambulances, ATF – responded.\"}, {\"start\": 40.68, \"end\": 48.0, \"text\": \"The suspect was captured a few hours later at a home not far from the school.\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 58.68, \"text\": \"Police say they were able to track the shooter down quickly because several students recognized\"}, {\"start\": 58.68, \"end\": 61.84, \"text\": \"him immediately as a former student.\"}, {\"start\": 61.84, \"end\": 66.96, \"text\": \"Law enforcement officials say there were numerous fatalities, however at the time of this recording,\"}, {\"start\": 66.96, \"end\": 79.84, \"text\": \"officials had not release exact number of people killed or injured but it is at least 16.\"}, {\"start\": 79.84, \"end\": 85.8, \"text\": \"Officials say this is the worst mass shooting in Broward County history.\"}, {\"start\": 88.72, \"end\": 95.68, \"text\": \"Last month “InTouch” magazine published a 2011 interview with former porn star Stephanie\"}, {\"start\": 95.68, \"end\": 113.32, \"text\": \"Clifford a.k.a. “Stormy Daniels.”\"}, {\"start\": 113.32, \"end\": 127.56, \"text\": \"She goes into detail about an extramarital affair she had with President Trump in 2006.\"}, {\"start\": 127.56, \"end\": 132.44, \"text\": \"Trump vehemently denies the encounter.\"}, {\"start\": 132.44, \"end\": 146.16, \"text\": \"But on Tuesday Trump’s long-time personal lawyer Michael Cohen made a stunning admission.\"}, {\"start\": 146.16, \"end\": 158.48, \"text\": \"He admitted he paid Clifford 130-thousand dollars out of his own pocket back in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 158.48, \"end\": 165.64, \"text\": \"Cohen says neither the Trump organization nor the Trump campaign played a role in the\"}, {\"start\": 165.64, \"end\": 168.4, \"text\": \"payment and that neither group reimbursed him.\"}, {\"start\": 168.4, \"end\": 175.6, \"text\": \"Cohen tells CNN he made the payment to protect Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 177.84, \"end\": 194.6, \"text\": \"Broadway actor Patrick Boll is among six men busted in a prostitution sting in Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 194.6, \"end\": 205.84, \"text\": \"Boll most recently appeared in a Broadway version of “Mamma Mia!” and he was also\"}, {\"start\": 205.84, \"end\": 214.76, \"text\": \"on TV shows like “Gossip Girl” and “The Good Wife.”\"}, {\"start\": 214.76, \"end\": 229.24, \"text\": \"According to Naples police, the 53-year-old offered money to an undercover cop for sexual acts.\"}, {\"start\": 229.24, \"end\": 249.16, \"text\": \"Boll was arrested alongside Lee County judge Jay Rosman, pastor Richard Cecil and three others.\"}, {\"start\": 251.92, \"end\": 260.2, \"text\": \"Twenty children have died from the flu so far this year, so recognizing early symptoms\"}, {\"start\": 260.2, \"end\": 265.96, \"text\": \"and signs of the flu are vital.\"}, {\"start\": 265.96, \"end\": 274.24, \"text\": \"Here are some warning signs: if your child is having trouble breathing, breathing fast,\"}, {\"start\": 274.24, \"end\": 286.88, \"text\": \"has bluish skin color, is not waking up or not interacting or is unusually irritable.\"}, {\"start\": 286.88, \"end\": 295.11, \"text\": \"Officials with the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) say as soon as you suspect\"}, {\"start\": 295.12, \"end\": 300.48, \"text\": \"your child may have the flu, call the doctor right away.\"}, {\"start\": 300.48, \"end\": 307.08, \"text\": \"Health officials say the best way for parents to protect their children is to get vaccinated\"}, {\"start\": 307.08, \"end\": 310.36, \"text\": \"every year.\"}, {\"start\": 312.92, \"end\": 323.24, \"text\": \"If you’re looking for temporary employment for the spring, Home Depot is hiring 80,000\"}, {\"start\": 323.24, \"end\": 324.84, \"text\": \"new employees.\"}, {\"start\": 325.04, \"end\": 330.88, \"text\": \"To help candidates supply, the company is allowing applicants to sign up online for\"}, {\"start\": 330.88, \"end\": 332.4, \"text\": \"in-person interviews.\"}, {\"start\": 332.4, \"end\": 339.96, \"text\": \"Job seekers must visit the company’s website and choose the most convenient interview time\"}, {\"start\": 339.96, \"end\": 343.0, \"text\": \"and location.\"}, {\"start\": 343.0, \"end\": 352.24, \"text\": \"The jobs are seasonal and will be available in many of the more than 2,000 Home Depot\"}, {\"start\": 352.24, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"locations.\"}, {\"start\": 356.88, \"end\": 372.84, \"text\": \"Former First Lady Michelle Obama tweeted: “Happy #Valentine’s Day to my one and\"}, {\"start\": 372.84, \"end\": 374.76, \"text\": \"only, @Barack Obama.\"}, {\"start\": 374.76, \"end\": 382.2, \"text\": \"To celebrate the occasion, I’m dedicating a little Valentine’s Day playlist to you!”\"}, {\"start\": 382.2, \"end\": 397.2, \"text\": \"The playlist includes songs such as “Fallin’ by Alicia Keys, “Halo” by Beyoncé and\"}, {\"start\": 397.2, \"end\": 409.28, \"text\": \"“Just The Way You Are” by Billy Joel.\"}, {\"start\": 409.28, \"end\": 417.88, \"text\": \"Former President Barack Obama also honored his wife on Valentine’s Day tweeting: “She\"}, {\"start\": 417.88, \"end\": 425.76, \"text\": \"makes every day and every place better.”\"}, {\"start\": 427.84, \"end\": 431.04, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 431.04, \"end\": 432.68, \"text\": \"I’m Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 432.68, \"end\": 435.32, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 435.32, \"end\": 440.68, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 440.68, \"end\": 445.48, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "aaOux6d7Ny4": {
    "video_id": "aaOux6d7Ny4",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.11.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180412",
    "duration": 789,
    "view_count": 1935,
    "description": "4.11.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-House Speaker Paul Ryan will step down \n-Trump considering firing Rod Rosenstein\n-Former House Speaker joins marijuana firm's board\n-Zuckerberg says his personal data was shared too \n-Mariah Carey reveals bipolar disorder battle\n-Road rage caught on cam, police need public's help\n-Man robs bank to impress Taylor Swift\n-Your National Pet Day pictures\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented s",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.46, \"end\": 9.2, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.2, \"end\": 10.94, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.94, \"end\": 12.56, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.56, \"end\": 15.72, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.84, \"end\": 24.98, \"text\": \"Big news on Capitol Hill today.\"}, {\"start\": 25.06, \"end\": 31.52, \"text\": \"House Speaker Paul Ryan announced he will not seek re-election as Congressman for Wisconsin's\"}, {\"start\": 31.52, \"end\": 42.74, \"text\": \"first district, a seat he's held since 1999.\"}, {\"start\": 42.74, \"end\": 51.22, \"text\": \"Ryan informed his staff and fellow Republican lawmakers before addressing the media.\"}, {\"start\": 51.22, \"end\": 57.04, \"text\": \"Ryan reminded everyone he initially did not want the job as House Speaker but reluctantly\"}, {\"start\": 57.04, \"end\": 64.02, \"text\": \"took it and gave it everything he had to give.\"}, {\"start\": 64.08, \"end\": 73.36, \"text\": \"But he was facing an uphill battle to retain the majority in the House and sources say\"}, {\"start\": 73.36, \"end\": 79.48, \"text\": \"he did not want to lead the Republican Party if it was a minority party.\"}, {\"start\": 79.48, \"end\": 83.48, \"text\": \"Ryan leaves Washington having accomplished one of his primary goals -- passing sweeping\"}, {\"start\": 83.48, \"end\": 87.16, \"text\": \"tax reform.\"}, {\"start\": 87.2, \"end\": 90.3, \"text\": \"Ryan now says he wants to spend more time with his family.\"}, {\"start\": 90.3, \"end\": 98.98, \"text\": \"He will serve out his full term before retiring in January.\"}, {\"start\": 98.98, \"end\": 110.66, \"text\": \"President Trump weighed in on Ryan's decision by tweeting: \\\"Speaker Paul Ryan is a truly\"}, {\"start\": 110.66, \"end\": 123.98, \"text\": \"good man, and while he will not be seeking re-election, he will leave a legacy of achievement\"}, {\"start\": 123.98, \"end\": 127.62, \"text\": \"that nobody can question.\"}, {\"start\": 127.62, \"end\": 130.06, \"text\": \"We are with you Paul!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 132.8, \"end\": 137.18, \"text\": \"There could be another big shakeup in Washington, DC.\"}, {\"start\": 137.18, \"end\": 144.26, \"text\": \"Multiple sources tell CNN President Trump is considering firing Deputy Attorney General\"}, {\"start\": 144.38, \"end\": 147.66, \"text\": \"Rod Rosenstein.\"}, {\"start\": 147.66, \"end\": 157.44, \"text\": \"He is a man who oversees Robert Mueller's Russia investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 157.58, \"end\": 166.34, \"text\": \"And many political analysts believe Trump's decision gained urgency after the FBI raids\"}, {\"start\": 166.34, \"end\": 175.18, \"text\": \"that targeted the president's personal attorney, Michael Cohen.\"}, {\"start\": 175.18, \"end\": 183.52, \"text\": \"The raids took place on the same day that President Trump's lawyers met with Mueller's team.\"}, {\"start\": 183.52, \"end\": 192.96, \"text\": \"Trump's legal team believes Rosenstein crossed the line when he approved the raids.\"}, {\"start\": 192.96, \"end\": 198.28, \"text\": \"They believe Rosenstein has a conflict of interest because he is a potential witness\"}, {\"start\": 198.28, \"end\": 201.6, \"text\": \"in Mueller's investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 205.98, \"end\": 220.34, \"text\": \"Former House Speaker John Boehner has done a 180 on his stance on legalization of marijuana.\"}, {\"start\": 220.34, \"end\": 229.6, \"text\": \"He announced on Twitter he's joining the Board of Directors of a cannabis company.\"}, {\"start\": 229.6, \"end\": 240.08, \"text\": \"\\\"Acreage Holdings\\\" is a multi-state cannabis business that aims to make cannabis available\"}, {\"start\": 240.08, \"end\": 245.0, \"text\": \"to any patient who can benefit from safe and reliable access.\"}, {\"start\": 245.0, \"end\": 251.88, \"text\": \"Boehner says he's joining the Board because his opinion on cannabis has evolved.\"}, {\"start\": 251.88, \"end\": 258.12, \"text\": \"In 2009 he was unalterably opposed to legalization of marijuana.\"}, {\"start\": 258.12, \"end\": 264.3, \"text\": \"But now he says he's convinced it should be legalized so more research can be done, it\"}, {\"start\": 264.3, \"end\": 271.06, \"text\": \"can help veterans and reverse the opioid epidemic ravaging communities.\"}, {\"start\": 273.82, \"end\": 284.62, \"text\": \"Facebook's founder and CEO Mark Zuckerberg was back on Capitol Hill today for round two.\"}, {\"start\": 284.62, \"end\": 293.06, \"text\": \"He's testifying before a House panel to address how Facebook mishandled the data tens of millions\"}, {\"start\": 293.06, \"end\": 296.02, \"text\": \"of users.\"}, {\"start\": 296.02, \"end\": 303.2, \"text\": \"Yesterday Zuckerberg admitted his company didn't do enough to protect the privacy of\"}, {\"start\": 303.2, \"end\": 305.3, \"text\": \"its users and he apologized.\"}, {\"start\": 305.3, \"end\": 309.82, \"text\": \"But today it was clear lawmakers wanted more than an apology.\"}, {\"start\": 309.86, \"end\": 319.14, \"text\": \"They wanted a better explanation of how Facebook got into a data scandal and political controversy.\"}, {\"start\": 319.2, \"end\": 325.56, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg did reveal that his own data was exposed as well and promised lawmakers a more\"}, {\"start\": 325.6, \"end\": 330.54, \"text\": \"proactive approach to security.\"}, {\"start\": 330.54, \"end\": 338.12, \"text\": \"But when one Senator asked if Zuckerberg was willing to change Facebook's business model\"}, {\"start\": 338.12, \"end\": 343.7, \"text\": \"in the interest of protecting individual privacy, Zuckerberg did not give a direct answer.\"}, {\"start\": 343.7, \"end\": 351.38, \"text\": \"That's when another congressperson said fix the problem before Congress overreacts and\"}, {\"start\": 351.38, \"end\": 354.64, \"text\": \"does it for him.\"}, {\"start\": 354.64, \"end\": 356.94, \"text\": \"But here's an interesting side note.\"}, {\"start\": 357.1, \"end\": 363.72, \"text\": \"Apparently investors were pleased with Zuckerberg's performance on Capitol Hill.\"}, {\"start\": 363.86, \"end\": 372.22, \"text\": \"Facebook stock rose 4.5% by the end of yesterday's hearing.\"}, {\"start\": 375.5, \"end\": 388.02, \"text\": \"Pop superstar Mariah Carey tells People magazine that she is bipolar and has been for years.\"}, {\"start\": 388.02, \"end\": 394.14, \"text\": \"Carey says she was first diagnosed in 2001 when she was hospitalized following a breakdown.\"}, {\"start\": 394.14, \"end\": 403.32, \"text\": \"But she lived in denial, isolation and in constant fear that someone would expose her.\"}, {\"start\": 403.32, \"end\": 408.08, \"text\": \"Carey says she couldn't carry the burden of that secret any longer.\"}, {\"start\": 408.08, \"end\": 414.2, \"text\": \"Now that she has sought treatment and surrounded yourself with positive people, she is proud\"}, {\"start\": 414.2, \"end\": 419.18, \"text\": \"to talk about her condition.\"}, {\"start\": 419.26, \"end\": 427.7, \"text\": \"Carey says she is now in therapy, taking medication and that is allowing her to get back to doing\"}, {\"start\": 427.7, \"end\": 433.68, \"text\": \"what she loves -- writing songs and making music.\"}, {\"start\": 437.42, \"end\": 447.08, \"text\": \"Police in Sarasota, Florida are looking for the driver that ran a motorcyclist off the road.\"}, {\"start\": 447.08, \"end\": 450.04, \"text\": \"Video of the incident was recorded by a motorist.\"}, {\"start\": 450.04, \"end\": 456.94, \"text\": \"It shows a motorcycle riding next to a Mazda hatchback.\"}, {\"start\": 456.96, \"end\": 463.5, \"text\": \"After the motorcycle driver appears to make contact with the Mazda, the car swerved into\"}, {\"start\": 463.52, \"end\": 468.74, \"text\": \"the bike, knocking the rider to the ground.\"}, {\"start\": 480.0, \"end\": 486.94, \"text\": \"Incredibly the motorcycle driver suffered only minor scrapes and bruises.\"}, {\"start\": 486.94, \"end\": 491.46, \"text\": \"It's not clear what started the incident.\"}, {\"start\": 491.46, \"end\": 496.72, \"text\": \"Police tweeted the video and are asking for the public's help in identifying the driver\"}, {\"start\": 496.72, \"end\": 499.54, \"text\": \"of the Mazda.\"}, {\"start\": 502.28, \"end\": 511.58, \"text\": \"Connecticut police say 26-year-old Bruce Rowley was arrested for robbing a bank.\"}, {\"start\": 511.58, \"end\": 521.32, \"text\": \"Rowley claims he did it to impress singer Taylor Swift.\"}, {\"start\": 521.32, \"end\": 529.5, \"text\": \"Officers in Rhode Island spotted Rowley the day after he robbed the bank because he was\"}, {\"start\": 529.5, \"end\": 532.98, \"text\": \"driving the same car used in the crime.\"}, {\"start\": 532.98, \"end\": 538.32, \"text\": \"Rowley led them on a chase that crossed over into Connecticut.\"}, {\"start\": 538.32, \"end\": 548.54, \"text\": \"Troopers were able to stop Rowley's car using spike strips.\"}, {\"start\": 548.54, \"end\": 558.66, \"text\": \"While transporting Rowley, police say he told them he had a crush on Taylor Swift and robbed\"}, {\"start\": 558.66, \"end\": 561.02, \"text\": \"the bank for her.\"}, {\"start\": 561.02, \"end\": 568.92, \"text\": \"He even threw some of the stolen money over her fence and tried to contact her, but she\"}, {\"start\": 568.92, \"end\": 570.98, \"text\": \"wasn't home.\"}, {\"start\": 570.98, \"end\": 577.62, \"text\": \"Rowley also claimed he was wanted to donate some of the money to the police department.\"}, {\"start\": 577.62, \"end\": 582.68, \"text\": \"Rowley was booked and is now being held on $100,000 bond.\"}, {\"start\": 585.1, \"end\": 594.02, \"text\": \"Earlier this week we asked you to send us pictures for National Pet Day today.\"}, {\"start\": 594.1, \"end\": 598.72, \"text\": \"And oh boy did you respond!\"}, {\"start\": 598.72, \"end\": 603.78, \"text\": \"We received dozens of adorable pictures that serve as a reminder that our pets are not\"}, {\"start\": 603.78, \"end\": 605.9, \"text\": \"just animals.\"}, {\"start\": 605.96, \"end\": 607.66, \"text\": \"They are family.\"}, {\"start\": 607.66, \"end\": 612.9, \"text\": \"They grow up with our children.\"}, {\"start\": 612.94, \"end\": 622.5, \"text\": \"Donna Gorlewski shared this picture of her son Bryan at six years old and their dog River\"}, {\"start\": 622.5, \"end\": 624.08, \"text\": \"at six months old.\"}, {\"start\": 624.08, \"end\": 630.86, \"text\": \"Then a decade later they were still by each other side, up until the day River died.\"}, {\"start\": 630.86, \"end\": 635.82, \"text\": \"This is Rolando Gutierrez's family picture.\"}, {\"start\": 635.84, \"end\": 643.78, \"text\": \"He says \\\"Skyla and Brooklyn are our everything.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 643.78, \"end\": 655.5, \"text\": \"Marsha Pennington-Turner says she and her cat Caspar watch Sign1News together on her iPad.\"}, {\"start\": 655.64, \"end\": 665.7, \"text\": \"And when Chris Webb went to Disneyland, her dogs Grom and Romeo went as well.\"}, {\"start\": 665.7, \"end\": 675.26, \"text\": \"Thank you for sharing your stories of love, laughter and a lifetime of memories with your pets.\"}, {\"start\": 675.3, \"end\": 681.84, \"text\": \"Now sit back and watch as we share all of the pictures you sent us.\"}, {\"start\": 681.92, \"end\": 686.4, \"text\": \"Happy National Pet day!\"}, {\"start\": 765.36, \"end\": 767.64, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 767.64, \"end\": 769.28, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 769.28, \"end\": 771.22, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 771.22, \"end\": 775.38, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 775.38, \"end\": 776.74, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 776.74, \"end\": 778.2, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 778.2, \"end\": 781.08, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "uiXnsEXuMVY": {
    "video_id": "uiXnsEXuMVY",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.1.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180302",
    "duration": 515,
    "view_count": 1360,
    "description": "3.1.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Bobby Brown says drugs didn’t kill Whitney Houston\n-Opioid epidemic at unprecedented levels\n-Trump’s son-in-law under the microscope again\n-Equifax hackers stole more than previously reported\n-DACA youth march from NY to DC\n-Uber will get patients to and from the doctor\n-Selfies make your nose look 30% bigger\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leade",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.98, \"end\": 8.84, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.84, \"end\": 11.14, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.16, \"end\": 12.74, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.74, \"end\": 15.28, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.64, \"end\": 31.18, \"text\": \"Six years after music icon Whitney Houston passed away, her husband Bobby Brown is talking\"}, {\"start\": 31.18, \"end\": 33.72, \"text\": \"about her death.\"}, {\"start\": 33.72, \"end\": 47.06, \"text\": \"He told Rolling Stone magazine that he doesn't think Houston's accidental drowning in 2012\"}, {\"start\": 47.06, \"end\": 50.02, \"text\": \"was caused by drugs.\"}, {\"start\": 50.02, \"end\": 54.7, \"text\": \"Brown said his ex-wife died of a broken heart.\"}, {\"start\": 54.7, \"end\": 59.42, \"text\": \"Brown was married to the superstar from 1992 to 2007.\"}, {\"start\": 59.42, \"end\": 68.48, \"text\": \"After Houston's death, an autopsy was conducted by the Los Angeles County coroner's office.\"}, {\"start\": 68.48, \"end\": 74.8, \"text\": \"They found cocaine in Houston's system when she died, along with marijuana, the anti-anxiety\"}, {\"start\": 74.8, \"end\": 86.28, \"text\": \"drug Xanax, the muscle relaxant Flexeril and the allergy medicine Benadryl.\"}, {\"start\": 86.28, \"end\": 94.56, \"text\": \"Brown also told Rolling Stone that he is still waiting for justice in the death of his daughter,\"}, {\"start\": 94.56, \"end\": 98.76, \"text\": \"Bobbi Kristina Brown, who died in 2015.\"}, {\"start\": 103.36, \"end\": 110.24, \"text\": \"The key players in the White House's fight to combat opioid abuse held a summit on Thursday\"}, {\"start\": 110.24, \"end\": 112.56, \"text\": \"to lay out the challenges that still remain.\"}, {\"start\": 112.56, \"end\": 120.2, \"text\": \"Several senior officials, as well as First Lady Melania Trump, stressed the importance\"}, {\"start\": 120.2, \"end\": 123.2, \"text\": \"of this effort.\"}, {\"start\": 123.2, \"end\": 133.6, \"text\": \"Attorney General Jeff Sessions said the opioid epidemic is unprecedented in the history of\"}, {\"start\": 133.62, \"end\": 136.799, \"text\": \"the country.\"}, {\"start\": 136.8, \"end\": 146.64, \"text\": \"Experts say more than 2 million Americans are dependent on prescription or street drugs.\"}, {\"start\": 146.64, \"end\": 155.16, \"text\": \"In 2016 alone, more than 42,000 Americans died from opioid overdoses and 236 million\"}, {\"start\": 155.16, \"end\": 160.88, \"text\": \"opioid prescriptions were dispensed in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 160.88, \"end\": 172.08, \"text\": \"The White House wants more funding for programs that help substance abusers and wants states\"}, {\"start\": 172.08, \"end\": 177.76, \"text\": \"to have more flexibility to treat users.\"}, {\"start\": 177.76, \"end\": 183.56, \"text\": \"The areas the White House is focusing on include education and prevention, law enforcement\"}, {\"start\": 183.56, \"end\": 185.68, \"text\": \"and treatment.\"}, {\"start\": 188.76, \"end\": 199.32, \"text\": \"President Trump's son-in-law Jared Kushner is once again finding himself under the microscope.\"}, {\"start\": 199.32, \"end\": 209.36, \"text\": \"The New York Times is reporting Kushner's family real estate group obtained several\"}, {\"start\": 209.36, \"end\": 215.76, \"text\": \"business loans after he met with company heads at the White House.\"}, {\"start\": 215.76, \"end\": 229.88, \"text\": \"According to the report, in November 2017 Apollo Global Management lent Kushner Companies\"}, {\"start\": 229.88, \"end\": 236.2, \"text\": \"$184 million to refinance the mortgage of a Chicago skyscraper after Kushner met with\"}, {\"start\": 236.2, \"end\": 240.32, \"text\": \"the founder of the company.\"}, {\"start\": 240.32, \"end\": 255.12, \"text\": \"And the Times reported in the spring of 2017, Citigroup lent Kushner Companies $325 million\"}, {\"start\": 255.12, \"end\": 262.28, \"text\": \"for some of its Brooklyn properties after Kushner met with the company CEO.\"}, {\"start\": 262.28, \"end\": 287.76, \"text\": \"A spokeswoman for Kushner's company said Kushner's White House position has no impact with the\"}, {\"start\": 287.76, \"end\": 291.08, \"text\": \"company's affairs with financial institutions.\"}, {\"start\": 294.08, \"end\": 304.44, \"text\": \"Last year Equifax announced that hackers stole the personal information of 145.5 million people.\"}, {\"start\": 304.44, \"end\": 310.84, \"text\": \"That included Social Security numbers, driver's license numbers and addresses.\"}, {\"start\": 310.84, \"end\": 316.12, \"text\": \"Now Equifax says it has discovered another 2.4 million Americans who had their names\"}, {\"start\": 316.12, \"end\": 322.84, \"text\": \"and driver's license numbers exposed.\"}, {\"start\": 322.88, \"end\": 330.28, \"text\": \"The company said it will notify the newly discovered victims and offer free identity\"}, {\"start\": 330.28, \"end\": 335.64, \"text\": \"theft protection and credit monitoring.\"}, {\"start\": 338.64, \"end\": 355.32, \"text\": \"On February 15th hundreds of undocumented young people and their supporters began a\"}, {\"start\": 355.32, \"end\": 360.2, \"text\": \"250-mile, 15-day march across six states to demand a clean Dream Act and draw attention\"}, {\"start\": 360.2, \"end\": 361.64, \"text\": \"to the struggles of dreamers.\"}, {\"start\": 361.76, \"end\": 365.92, \"text\": \"The march started in New York and ended in Washington DC today, where they held a protest\"}, {\"start\": 365.92, \"end\": 368.76, \"text\": \"in front of the Capitol.\"}, {\"start\": 368.76, \"end\": 375.68, \"text\": \"President Trump has said he would end the DACA program on March 5th.\"}, {\"start\": 375.68, \"end\": 386.28, \"text\": \"Protesters are hoping their march will inspire others to speak out to prevent that from happening.\"}, {\"start\": 389.64, \"end\": 399.32, \"text\": \"Every year millions of Americans miss medical appointments because they don't have transportation.\"}, {\"start\": 399.32, \"end\": 409.0, \"text\": \"The missed appointments cost the medical system more than $150 billion a year.\"}, {\"start\": 409.0, \"end\": 417.6, \"text\": \"So Uber Health is partnering with healthcare providers to schedule rides for patients.\"}, {\"start\": 417.6, \"end\": 424.639, \"text\": \"So far more than 100 healthcare organizations are on board, including hospitals, rehab centers,\"}, {\"start\": 424.64, \"end\": 431.16, \"text\": \"senior care facilities and physical therapy centers.\"}, {\"start\": 431.16, \"end\": 436.4, \"text\": \"The healthcare provider covers the cost for the ride.\"}, {\"start\": 440.32, \"end\": 448.28, \"text\": \"According to a recent poll conducted by the American Academy of Facial Plastic and Reconstructive\"}, {\"start\": 448.28, \"end\": 453.759, \"text\": \"surgeons, 55% of surgeons reported having patients who said they were seeking cosmetic\"}, {\"start\": 453.76, \"end\": 457.48, \"text\": \"surgery to make them look better in selfies.\"}, {\"start\": 457.48, \"end\": 462.44, \"text\": \"Don't make your final decision on plastic surgery based on your selfie, especially if\"}, {\"start\": 462.44, \"end\": 465.92, \"text\": \"you're considering getting a nose job.\"}, {\"start\": 465.92, \"end\": 472.48, \"text\": \"Researchers say selfies can make your nose look roughly 30% larger than it actually is.\"}, {\"start\": 472.48, \"end\": 478.4, \"text\": \"That's because the camera is closer to your nose than to the rest of your face.\"}, {\"start\": 478.4, \"end\": 480.0, \"text\": \"The solution?\"}, {\"start\": 480.0, \"end\": 487.44, \"text\": \"Take the selfie from a distance of 5 feet and the distortion isn't nearly as significant.\"}, {\"start\": 490.0, \"end\": 492.24, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 492.24, \"end\": 493.84, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 493.84, \"end\": 496.64, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 496.64, \"end\": 502.08, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 502.08, \"end\": 508.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "XkecBlYcxp4": {
    "video_id": "XkecBlYcxp4",
    "title": "California zoos welcome baby giraffe and meerkat mob (ASL - 3.16.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180316",
    "duration": 74,
    "view_count": 394,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.7, \"end\": 12.12, \"text\": \"The Santa Barbara zoo welcomed the birth of a new giraffe calf -- and she came early.\"}, {\"start\": 12.14, \"end\": 15.46, \"text\": \"She wasn't expected until next month.\"}, {\"start\": 15.46, \"end\": 22.6, \"text\": \"But zoo staff say mom and baby are bonding and doing well.\"}, {\"start\": 22.6, \"end\": 27.34, \"text\": \"Now the zoo is hosting a public contest to name the calf.\"}, {\"start\": 27.34, \"end\": 42.68, \"text\": \"So far, the names in the running are Amirah, Makena, Quinton and Nugget.\"}, {\"start\": 42.68, \"end\": 52.44, \"text\": \"A few miles away, the Los Angeles zoo debuted a new mob of meerkats.\"}, {\"start\": 52.44, \"end\": 59.4, \"text\": \"The zoo has been working with a breeding group and are hoping these meerkats will make more\"}, {\"start\": 59.4, \"end\": 60.96, \"text\": \"meerkats.\"}, {\"start\": 60.96, \"end\": 64.44, \"text\": \"The zoo is now home to three new females and for males.\"}, {\"start\": 64.44, \"end\": 70.24, \"text\": \"And according to the zoo, they are getting along with one another \\\"very well\\\"...\"}, {\"start\": 70.3, \"end\": 72.42, \"text\": \"...if you know what we me.\"}]"
  },
  "SZcnservpiE": {
    "video_id": "SZcnservpiE",
    "title": "Torture house kids only allowed to look at food (ASL - 1.19.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180120",
    "duration": 138,
    "view_count": 593,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.44, \"end\": 13.74, \"text\": \"We're learning more disturbing details about the physical and emotional abuse 13 children\"}, {\"start\": 13.86, \"end\": 23.14, \"text\": \"suffered at the hands of their parents.\"}, {\"start\": 23.14, \"end\": 28.88, \"text\": \"Officials in California say the children, ages 2 to 29, were not allowed to shower more\"}, {\"start\": 28.88, \"end\": 40.98, \"text\": \"than once a year, they were chained and padlocked to their beds and there were unopened toys\"}, {\"start\": 40.98, \"end\": 46.12, \"text\": \"in the house the children were not allowed to play with.\"}, {\"start\": 46.12, \"end\": 56.44, \"text\": \"The parents would buy food like apple or pumpkin pie and leave them on the counter for the\"}, {\"start\": 56.44, \"end\": 60.32, \"text\": \"children to look at but not eat.\"}, {\"start\": 60.32, \"end\": 71.28, \"text\": \"The 12 older children were so malnourished and small, doctors were shocked at their actual\"}, {\"start\": 71.28, \"end\": 74.72, \"text\": \"ages.\"}, {\"start\": 74.72, \"end\": 81.44, \"text\": \"The children lacked even the most basic life knowledge.\"}, {\"start\": 81.44, \"end\": 91.42, \"text\": \"Many of them didn't know what a police officer was or what medicine looked like.\"}, {\"start\": 91.42, \"end\": 102.6, \"text\": \"Police also learned the 17-year-old girl that escaped had been working on an escape plan\"}, {\"start\": 102.6, \"end\": 106.42, \"text\": \"with her siblings for more than two years.\"}, {\"start\": 106.42, \"end\": 126.54, \"text\": \"On Thursday the parents, David and Louise Turpin, pleaded not guilty to all charges,\"}, {\"start\": 126.54, \"end\": 130.48, \"text\": \"including 12 counts of false imprisonment and 12 counts of torture.\"}, {\"start\": 130.48, \"end\": 137.64, \"text\": \"They are each being held on $12 million bail.\"}]"
  },
  "2AWyzSyzrtk": {
    "video_id": "2AWyzSyzrtk",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.23.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180224",
    "duration": 448,
    "view_count": 1425,
    "description": "2.23.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Vehicle rams White House barricade\n-Teachers with guns: opinions split\n-FL sergeant gets emotional during press conference \n-Rick Gates pleads guilty \n-Jane Seymour poses for Playboy at 67 years old\n-Wakanda vs Wacounda, IL\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News prov",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.12, \"end\": 9.32, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.32, \"end\": 11.34, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.34, \"end\": 12.76, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.76, \"end\": 15.68, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.5, \"end\": 23.2, \"text\": \"The White House was briefly placed on lockdown today after a woman drove a vehicle into the\"}, {\"start\": 23.2, \"end\": 27.14, \"text\": \"building's barricades at the front of the gate.\"}, {\"start\": 27.14, \"end\": 29.66, \"text\": \"Police say this was not an accident.\"}, {\"start\": 29.66, \"end\": 34.2, \"text\": \"The woman smashed the barricade intentionally but she did not breach the barrier.\"}, {\"start\": 34.2, \"end\": 36.32, \"text\": \"The woman was arrested immediately.\"}, {\"start\": 36.32, \"end\": 39.0, \"text\": \"No shots were fired.\"}, {\"start\": 39.0, \"end\": 43.44, \"text\": \"Officials with the Secret Service say they are familiar with the driver and that she\"}, {\"start\": 43.44, \"end\": 46.32, \"text\": \"suffers from mental illness.\"}, {\"start\": 46.32, \"end\": 50.96, \"text\": \"They say her anger was not directed at President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 50.96, \"end\": 55.44, \"text\": \"The president was in the White House at the time of the incident.\"}, {\"start\": 57.92, \"end\": 64.96, \"text\": \"President Trump says he's focused on making schools safer.\"}, {\"start\": 64.96, \"end\": 72.4, \"text\": \"One idea under consideration: having teachers carry guns on a voluntary basis.\"}, {\"start\": 72.4, \"end\": 75.36, \"text\": \"Some teachers are not on board.\"}, {\"start\": 75.36, \"end\": 86.08, \"text\": \"The American Federation of Teachers released a statement Thursday that said \\\"teachers don't\"}, {\"start\": 86.08, \"end\": 91.84, \"text\": \"want to be armed, we want to teach.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 91.84, \"end\": 102.24, \"text\": \"And there's a new social media movement with a hashtag \\\"Arm Me With,\\\" where teachers list\"}, {\"start\": 102.24, \"end\": 107.49, \"text\": \"the things they would rather have than weapons.\"}, {\"start\": 107.49, \"end\": 114.85, \"text\": \"But some support the idea of guns in the classroom.\"}, {\"start\": 114.85, \"end\": 126.27, \"text\": \"Ohio Sheriff Richard Hones says he had 300 teachers sign up in less than eight hours,\"}, {\"start\": 126.27, \"end\": 130.009, \"text\": \"saying they want to have guns and be trained in firearms.\"}, {\"start\": 130.009, \"end\": 133.53, \"text\": \"We would love to hear your thoughts on this debate.\"}, {\"start\": 133.53, \"end\": 137.44, \"text\": \"Do you think school teachers should be armed?\"}, {\"start\": 137.44, \"end\": 142.8, \"text\": \"Would schools be safer if teachers were armed?\"}, {\"start\": 145.52, \"end\": 159.12, \"text\": \"Police officers and firefighters from Coral Springs who responded to the shooting at Marjory\"}, {\"start\": 159.12, \"end\": 165.64, \"text\": \"Stoneman Douglas high school are now sharing their stories.\"}, {\"start\": 165.64, \"end\": 169.76, \"text\": \"And as you can see, some officers were overcome with emotions.\"}, {\"start\": 169.76, \"end\": 176.0, \"text\": \"This is Sergeant Jeff Heinrich.\"}, {\"start\": 176.0, \"end\": 181.04, \"text\": \"His wife and son were in the school during the shooting rampage.\"}, {\"start\": 181.04, \"end\": 187.2, \"text\": \"He was overcome with emotions as he tried to share his experience.\"}, {\"start\": 187.2, \"end\": 197.76, \"text\": \"He said his wife and son were at opposite ends of the school when the shooting started\"}, {\"start\": 197.76, \"end\": 202.32, \"text\": \"but somehow they found each other and hid in a safe place together.\"}, {\"start\": 202.32, \"end\": 210.08, \"text\": \"Heinrich said once he learned his family was okay, he was able to focus on the task at\"}, {\"start\": 210.08, \"end\": 215.2, \"text\": \"hand -- finding and stopping the shooter.\"}, {\"start\": 217.36, \"end\": 229.92, \"text\": \"Rick Gates pleaded guilty Friday to conspiracy and making a false statement.\"}, {\"start\": 229.92, \"end\": 238.64, \"text\": \"Gates was one of Donald Trump's top aides during his presidential campaign.\"}, {\"start\": 238.64, \"end\": 243.349, \"text\": \"Gates is now the third associate of President Trump to make a deal with Special Counsel\"}, {\"start\": 243.349, \"end\": 246.93, \"text\": \"Robert Mueller.\"}, {\"start\": 246.96, \"end\": 252.24, \"text\": \"Mueller is investigating Russia meddling in the 2016 election.\"}, {\"start\": 252.24, \"end\": 260.0, \"text\": \"Mueller filed new charges on Thursday against Gates and former Trump campaign chairman Paul\"}, {\"start\": 260.0, \"end\": 262.34, \"text\": \"Manafort.\"}, {\"start\": 262.34, \"end\": 285.36, \"text\": \"Prosecutors say the two laundered $30 million, failed to pay taxes for almost 10 years and\"}, {\"start\": 285.36, \"end\": 295.6, \"text\": \"used real estate they owned to fraudulently secure more than $20 million in loans.\"}, {\"start\": 297.44, \"end\": 309.6, \"text\": \"67-year-old actress Jane Seymour says she feels sexier than ever and she's proving it\"}, {\"start\": 309.6, \"end\": 316.18, \"text\": \"by posing for Playboy.\"}, {\"start\": 316.18, \"end\": 321.1, \"text\": \"Seymour's new pictures will not be nude but she told the magazine that she feels comfortable\"}, {\"start\": 321.1, \"end\": 324.86, \"text\": \"in her own skin.\"}, {\"start\": 324.86, \"end\": 330.98, \"text\": \"This photo shoot comes 45 years after she first appeared in the magazine.\"}, {\"start\": 331.02, \"end\": 339.56, \"text\": \"Seymour currently stars in the TV sitcom \\\"Let's Get Physical.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 340.94, \"end\": 353.46, \"text\": \"Fans of the movie \\\"Black Panther\\\" won't leave the small town of Wauconda, Illinois alone.\"}, {\"start\": 353.46, \"end\": 360.4, \"text\": \"Officials in the small town have been getting some curious calls from fans of the film.\"}, {\"start\": 360.4, \"end\": 370.84, \"text\": \"The executive assistant to the mayor told the Hollywood Reporter one caller grilled\"}, {\"start\": 370.84, \"end\": 374.76, \"text\": \"her about where the town was hiding its vibranium.\"}, {\"start\": 374.76, \"end\": 385.6, \"text\": \"Vibranium is a fictional metal from the movie known for being stronger than any other.\"}, {\"start\": 385.6, \"end\": 393.76, \"text\": \"Another caller reportedly phoned just to confirm the town's pronunciation, then shouted\"}, {\"start\": 393.76, \"end\": 398.34, \"text\": \"\\\"Wakanda forever!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 398.34, \"end\": 406.14, \"text\": \"There was also a suggestion to change the town's high school mascot to...\"}, {\"start\": 406.14, \"end\": 410.5, \"text\": \"you guessed it...a black panther.\"}, {\"start\": 410.5, \"end\": 418.66, \"text\": \"But the school's principal said the current mascot, a bulldog, will remain for now.\"}, {\"start\": 421.48, \"end\": 423.78, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 423.78, \"end\": 425.18, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 425.189, \"end\": 428.33, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 428.33, \"end\": 433.76, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 433.76, \"end\": 440.02, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "9QZI0vEt4GQ": {
    "video_id": "9QZI0vEt4GQ",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.26.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171027",
    "duration": 460,
    "view_count": 215,
    "description": "October 26, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-THE OPIOD CRISIS IN AMERICA\n-HOUSE VOTES ON BUDGET RESOLUTION\n-TROOPER SAVES CHOKING MAN\n-RACIST CORN POPS ART\n-UBER ADDS A NEW FEATURE\n-FREE TACOS AT TACO BELL\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN, FOX, ABC, CBS, TBN (TRINITY BROADCAST NETW",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.0, \"end\": 22.0, \"text\": \"Today President Trump declared war on\"}, {\"start\": 22.0, \"end\": 26.0, \"text\": \"the opioid epidemic.\"}, {\"start\": 27.0, \"end\": 32.0, \"text\": \"He called the epidemic a public health emergency instead of a national\"}, {\"start\": 32.0, \"end\": 37.0, \"text\": \"emergency. Declaring a national emergency would allow the government to\"}, {\"start\": 37.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"tap into federal disaster relief funds -- money used for natural disasters like\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 46.0, \"text\": \"hurricanes. Under the Public Health Services\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 51.0, \"text\": \"Act federal agencies will be directed to give more grant money\"}, {\"start\": 51.0, \"end\": 57.0, \"text\": \"to fight the epidemic.\"}, {\"start\": 57.0, \"end\": 62.0, \"text\": \"While no additional federal funding will be automatically\"}, {\"start\": 62.0, \"end\": 67.0, \"text\": \"directed to the crisis, it will allow lawmakers to increase federal funding for\"}, {\"start\": 67.0, \"end\": 71.0, \"text\": \"fighting the problem. The impact of opioid\"}, {\"start\": 72.0, \"end\": 77.0, \"text\": \"addictions has affected many in the U.S. Officials say the\"}, {\"start\": 77.0, \"end\": 82.0, \"text\": \"number of deaths related to opioid overdoses\"}, {\"start\": 82.0, \"end\": 87.0, \"text\": \"is four times the amount it was\"}, {\"start\": 87.0, \"end\": 92.0, \"text\": \"in 1999. According to the Centers\"}, {\"start\": 92.0, \"end\": 95.0, \"text\": \"for Disease Control\"}, {\"start\": 95.0, \"end\": 100.0, \"text\": \"and Prevention more than 140 Americans die\"}, {\"start\": 100.0, \"end\": 108.0, \"text\": \"every day from an opioid overdose.\"}, {\"start\": 112.0, \"end\": 116.0, \"text\": \"Today the House votes on a budget resolution\"}, {\"start\": 116.0, \"end\": 121.0, \"text\": \"that would allow Congress to fast track\"}, {\"start\": 121.0, \"end\": 127.0, \"text\": \"a tax reform bill.\"}, {\"start\": 128.0, \"end\": 131.0, \"text\": \"Lawmakers are at odds over eliminating a popular tax\"}, {\"start\": 132.0, \"end\": 137.0, \"text\": \"deduction that people can take for state and local taxes that they\"}, {\"start\": 137.0, \"end\": 141.0, \"text\": \"pay. Some Republicans are threatening to vote\"}, {\"start\": 141.0, \"end\": 147.0, \"text\": \"with Democrats and oppose the budget.\"}, {\"start\": 147.0, \"end\": 151.0, \"text\": \"Cutting the deduction would help Republicans raise more\"}, {\"start\": 152.0, \"end\": 157.0, \"text\": \"than a trillion dollars to help pay for tax cuts over the next\"}, {\"start\": 157.0, \"end\": 162.0, \"text\": \"10 years. But Republicans from states with high\"}, {\"start\": 162.0, \"end\": 165.0, \"text\": \"taxes like New York, New Jersey,\"}, {\"start\": 166.0, \"end\": 171.0, \"text\": \"Illinois and California\"}, {\"start\": 171.0, \"end\": 177.0, \"text\": \"argue that their constituents rely on the deduction.\"}, {\"start\": 180.0, \"end\": 182.0, \"text\": \"An incredible thing happened Sunday\"}, {\"start\": 183.0, \"end\": 185.0, \"text\": \"in Rockaway Township New Jersey.\"}, {\"start\": 190.0, \"end\": 198.0, \"text\": \"A state trooper\"}, {\"start\": 198.0, \"end\": 204.0, \"text\": \"named Dennis Palaia\"}, {\"start\": 204.0, \"end\": 208.0, \"text\": \"was enjoying a Sunday off with his son\"}, {\"start\": 209.0, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"at Buffalo Wild Wings.\"}, {\"start\": 217.0, \"end\": 222.0, \"text\": \"Palaia noticed something wrong at the table\"}, {\"start\": 222.0, \"end\": 226.0, \"text\": \"behind him. A man was in distress and began showing visible signs that\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 231.0, \"text\": \"he couldn't breathe. Trooper Palaia quickly wrapped his arms around the man's\"}, {\"start\": 231.0, \"end\": 236.0, \"text\": \"waist and performed the Heimlich maneuver which cleared the man's airway.\"}, {\"start\": 236.0, \"end\": 241.0, \"text\": \"The man made a quick recovery thanks to the\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 244.0, \"text\": \"quick thinking of Trooper Palaia.\"}, {\"start\": 247.0, \"end\": 252.0, \"text\": \"Kellogg, the world's largest\"}, {\"start\": 252.0, \"end\": 256.0, \"text\": \"cereal maker, is changing the design of its\"}, {\"start\": 256.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"Corn Pops cereal boxes after a complaint\"}, {\"start\": 261.0, \"end\": 266.0, \"text\": \"that the art is racially\"}, {\"start\": 267.0, \"end\": 271.0, \"text\": \"offensive.\"}, {\"start\": 272.0, \"end\": 276.0, \"text\": \"On the box a little corn pop characters is doing different\"}, {\"start\": 276.0, \"end\": 280.0, \"text\": \"activities like shopping and playing in the arcade.\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"One Twitter user was offended by\"}, {\"start\": 287.0, \"end\": 295.0, \"text\": \"the character with a darker yellow tone. It was cleaning.\"}, {\"start\": 297.0, \"end\": 301.0, \"text\": \"The Twitter user said that it was teaching\"}, {\"start\": 301.0, \"end\": 305.0, \"text\": \"kids racism.\"}, {\"start\": 306.0, \"end\": 310.0, \"text\": \"Kellogg's apologized for the image and said\"}, {\"start\": 310.0, \"end\": 317.0, \"text\": \"it was updating its artwork. Kellogg's says the new artwork will reach stores soon.\"}, {\"start\": 319.0, \"end\": 324.0, \"text\": \"Uber has added a new feature that will make\"}, {\"start\": 325.0, \"end\": 329.0, \"text\": \"running errands or picking up friends easier.\"}, {\"start\": 329.0, \"end\": 334.0, \"text\": \"Uber customers will be able to add up to\"}, {\"start\": 334.0, \"end\": 339.0, \"text\": \"three separate stops. Users will also be able to make changes while they are on their\"}, {\"start\": 339.0, \"end\": 344.0, \"text\": \"Uber trip by adding or removing stops.\"}, {\"start\": 346.0, \"end\": 349.0, \"text\": \"The feature will became available today. If you have the latest version\"}, {\"start\": 349.0, \"end\": 356.0, \"text\": \"of the Uber app it will update automatically.\"}, {\"start\": 358.001, \"end\": 360.999, \"text\": \"Taco Bell\"}, {\"start\": 361.0, \"end\": 365.0, \"text\": \"is giving away free tacos as part of its annual\"}, {\"start\": 366.0, \"end\": 370.0, \"text\": \"promotion entitled \\\"Steal a base,\"}, {\"start\": 370.0, \"end\": 374.0, \"text\": \"steal a taco.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 374.001, \"end\": 378.999, \"text\": \"If Cameron\"}, {\"start\": 379.0, \"end\": 384.0, \"text\": \"Maybin helps the Astros\"}, {\"start\": 384.0, \"end\": 391.0, \"text\": \"win game two of the World Series,\"}, {\"start\": 391.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"free tacos for everyone!\"}, {\"start\": 398.001, \"end\": 402.0, \"text\": \"On Wednesday night Maybin stole a\"}, {\"start\": 402.0, \"end\": 406.0, \"text\": \"base in the 11th inning so Taco Bell will hand out free\"}, {\"start\": 407.0, \"end\": 412.0, \"text\": \"Doritos Locos tacos\"}, {\"start\": 412.0, \"end\": 418.0, \"text\": \"on November 1st. You can get a free\"}, {\"start\": 418.024, \"end\": 426.024, \"text\": \"taco between 2pm and 6pm.\"}, {\"start\": 428.0, \"end\": 431.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 431.0, \"end\": 433.0, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 433.0, \"end\": 436.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 437.0, \"end\": 444.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 445.0, \"end\": 452.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "CHLpAQvilH0": {
    "video_id": "CHLpAQvilH0",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.8.2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171209",
    "duration": 465,
    "view_count": 630,
    "description": "December 8, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-SNOW STORM MOVING ACROSS THE SOUTHEAST\n-EMAIL SHOWS EFFORT TO GIVE TRUMP CAMP WIKILEAKS DOCS\n-TRUMP SUPPORTS ROY MOORE\n-JERUSALEM EMBASSY WILL NOT MOVE THIS YEAR\n-FIRES CONTINUE IN SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN, FO",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.3, \"end\": 9.48, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.5, \"end\": 10.64, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 10.7, \"end\": 12.72, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.56, \"end\": 23.42, \"text\": \"A rare winter storm struck this weekend --\"}, {\"start\": 23.48, \"end\": 33.32, \"text\": \"covering a 2,200 mile path from the deep South to the Northeast.\"}, {\"start\": 33.32, \"end\": 38.72, \"text\": \"For many states it was the first snowstorm of the season.\"}, {\"start\": 38.76, \"end\": 44.96, \"text\": \"The snow is expected to melt in Louisiana and Mississippi later this afternoon.\"}, {\"start\": 44.96, \"end\": 59.32, \"text\": \"But a rain-snow mix will continue to fall from central Alabama to north Georgia into the evening.\"}, {\"start\": 59.36, \"end\": 66.68, \"text\": \"Forecasters say snow will continue to fall in the northern states -- New Jersey, Pennsylvania,\"}, {\"start\": 66.72, \"end\": 70.24, \"text\": \"Maryland and Delaware.\"}, {\"start\": 70.32, \"end\": 75.76, \"text\": \"And snow is still falling in northwest Atlanta.\"}, {\"start\": 75.84, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"A winter storm warning is in effect for all of Georgia.\"}, {\"start\": 81.12, \"end\": 85.76, \"text\": \"The winter storm warning will remain in place for the metro Atlanta area\"}, {\"start\": 85.8, \"end\": 87.28, \"text\": \"until Saturday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 89.96, \"end\": 97.04, \"text\": \"An email given to Congressional investigators show that members of the Trump campaign\"}, {\"start\": 97.08, \"end\": 106.67, \"text\": \"were offered a website address and decryption key\"}, {\"start\": 106.68, \"end\": 116.28, \"text\": \"that would give them access to hacked WikiLeaks documents.\"}, {\"start\": 116.4, \"end\": 128.68, \"text\": \"Then-candidate Donald Trump, his son Donald Trump, Jr and others in the Trump organization\"}, {\"start\": 128.72, \"end\": 135.08, \"text\": \"received the email on September 4, 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 135.16, \"end\": 141.95, \"text\": \"But it's not clear whether the email was a real effort to give the\"}, {\"start\": 141.96, \"end\": 147.76, \"text\": \"hacked documents to the Trump campaign.\"}, {\"start\": 147.88, \"end\": 154.0, \"text\": \"It came from someone who listed his name as \\\"Mike Erickson\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 154.08, \"end\": 158.56, \"text\": \"and investigators aren't sure who the sender is.\"}, {\"start\": 158.76, \"end\": 165.68, \"text\": \"CNN was unable to make contact with the individual.\"}, {\"start\": 165.8, \"end\": 173.76, \"text\": \"Trump, Jr. told investigators he had no recollection of the email\"}, {\"start\": 173.8, \"end\": 179.48, \"text\": \"but it was described by multiple sources\"}, {\"start\": 179.56, \"end\": 187.36, \"text\": \"and its existence was verified by Trump, Jr.'s attorney.\"}, {\"start\": 187.44, \"end\": 194.56, \"text\": \"Congressional investigators are trying to determine whether the individual who sent\"}, {\"start\": 194.56, \"end\": 203.56, \"text\": \"the September email is legitimate.\"}, {\"start\": 205.6, \"end\": 210.08, \"text\": \"President Trump is heading to Florida tonight for a campaign-style rally\"}, {\"start\": 210.12, \"end\": 215.36, \"text\": \"in support of Roy Moore.\"}, {\"start\": 215.4, \"end\": 222.599, \"text\": \"The U.S. Senate special election in Alabama is just two days away and Trump has put his\"}, {\"start\": 222.6, \"end\": 227.92, \"text\": \"full endorsement behind the embattled Republican candidate.\"}, {\"start\": 228.0, \"end\": 236.64, \"text\": \"Capitol Hill is still reeling from a wave of sexual misconduct allegations and resignations\"}, {\"start\": 236.72, \"end\": 246.44, \"text\": \"including Democratic Senator Al Franken, Democratic Congressman John Conyers\"}, {\"start\": 246.44, \"end\": 255.8, \"text\": \"and Republican Congressman Trent Franks.\"}, {\"start\": 255.88, \"end\": 261.12, \"text\": \"Moore faces multiple allegations of pursuing relationships with teenaged girls while he\"}, {\"start\": 261.16, \"end\": 265.64, \"text\": \"was in his 30s and of assault by two of them.\"}, {\"start\": 265.76, \"end\": 277.24, \"text\": \"Moore's accuser, Beverly Young Nelson, held a press conference in Atlanta today.\"}, {\"start\": 277.32, \"end\": 284.68, \"text\": \"During the press conference Nelson said she is a Republican who voted from Trump\"}, {\"start\": 284.68, \"end\": 295.04, \"text\": \"but Trump has chosen to support a powerful politician like Moore over women like her.\"}, {\"start\": 295.08, \"end\": 301.68, \"text\": \"The Republican National Convention is throwing his support behind Moore.\"}, {\"start\": 304.4, \"end\": 312.08, \"text\": \"President Trump announced Wednesday that the U.S. Embassy in Israel will move\"}, {\"start\": 312.12, \"end\": 319.76, \"text\": \"from Tel Aviv to Jerusalem.\"}, {\"start\": 319.76, \"end\": 327.64, \"text\": \"The decision has sparked protests in the Middle East and beyond, sparking concerns that chances\"}, {\"start\": 327.72, \"end\": 334.6, \"text\": \"at a permanent peace in the region are fading.\"}, {\"start\": 334.6, \"end\": 342.52, \"text\": \"But when exactly will the embassy move?\"}, {\"start\": 342.6, \"end\": 355.56, \"text\": \"Speaking in Paris Friday, Secretary of State Rex Tiller said said it will take a while.\"}, {\"start\": 358.52, \"end\": 369.16, \"text\": \"A number of wildfires in Southern California continue to pose a major threat to residents\"}, {\"start\": 369.16, \"end\": 377.52, \"text\": \"in the area as firefighters are working around the clock to contain the blazes.\"}, {\"start\": 377.52, \"end\": 383.0, \"text\": \"The sheer size of the California wildfires, paired with unfavorable conditions, is creating\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 387.08, \"text\": \"a tough environment for officials on the ground.\"}, {\"start\": 387.32, \"end\": 393.8, \"text\": \"The biggest of the six blazes raging in Southern California is more than twice the size of\"}, {\"start\": 393.84, \"end\": 411.24, \"text\": \"Washington D.C. and is the biggest fire Los Angeles has battled since 1961.\"}, {\"start\": 411.4, \"end\": 417.56, \"text\": \"At least 190,000 people have been evacuated from their homes.\"}, {\"start\": 417.68, \"end\": 424.36, \"text\": \"Five-thousand seven hundred firefighters working to contain the fires.\"}, {\"start\": 424.4, \"end\": 432.479, \"text\": \"On Friday President Trump approved an emergency declaration freeing up federal funds.\"}, {\"start\": 432.48, \"end\": 441.2, \"text\": \"Thirteen-hundred California national guardsmen have been activated.\"}, {\"start\": 443.04, \"end\": 444.64, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 444.8, \"end\": 445.76, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 445.84, \"end\": 448.4, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 448.48, \"end\": 452.48, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 452.64, \"end\": 457.68, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "6aLr21Iza1U": {
    "video_id": "6aLr21Iza1U",
    "title": "It’s National Soft Ice Cream Day! (ASL - 8.19.19)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20190820",
    "duration": 61,
    "view_count": 196,
    "description": "Transcript\n\nIt's a great day to beat the heat with a delicious treat.\n\nToday is National Softserve Ice Cream day.\n\nHere's a fun fact: the secret ingredient behind softserve ice cream is air.\n\nAccording to the Smithsonian Institute, that's what brings out the creamy texture.\n\nMore than a few people claim to have created the dessert.\n\nBut we know people around the world have been enjoying this delicacy since the 1940s.\n\nSo take a break and grab your favorite flavor!\n\nIt's a holiday after all.\n\nThe",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.78, \"end\": 7.68, \"text\": \"It's a great day to beat the heat with a delicious treat.\"}, {\"start\": 7.68, \"end\": 10.52, \"text\": \"Today is National Softserve Ice Cream day.\"}, {\"start\": 10.52, \"end\": 18.36, \"text\": \"Here's a fun fact: the secret ingredient behind softserve ice cream is air.\"}, {\"start\": 18.36, \"end\": 28.18, \"text\": \"According to the Smithsonian Institute, that's what brings out the creamy texture.\"}, {\"start\": 28.18, \"end\": 37.98, \"text\": \"More than a few people claim to have created the dessert.\"}, {\"start\": 38.0, \"end\": 46.0, \"text\": \"But we know people around the world have been enjoying this delicacy since the 1940s.\"}, {\"start\": 46.06, \"end\": 51.14, \"text\": \"So take a break and grab your favorite flavor!\"}, {\"start\": 51.14, \"end\": 60.5, \"text\": \"It's a holiday after all.\"}]"
  },
  "tpazvXGyir0": {
    "video_id": "tpazvXGyir0",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.24.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180425",
    "duration": 399,
    "view_count": 1072,
    "description": "4.24.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Prince's family sues hospital, Walgreens\n-\"Avengers\" movie marathon!\n-State lawmakers honor Waffle House hero\n-Toronto van attack suspect charged \n-Former President Bush alert and talking\n-Veteran gets world's first total penile transplant\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.56, \"end\": 8.62, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.62, \"end\": 11.22, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.26, \"end\": 12.68, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.68, \"end\": 15.9, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.32, \"end\": 35.04, \"text\": \"The family of music legend Prince is suing Walgreens pharmacy and Illinois' Trinity Medical\"}, {\"start\": 35.04, \"end\": 37.28, \"text\": \"Center in the singer's 2016 overdose death.\"}, {\"start\": 37.28, \"end\": 44.34, \"text\": \"The wrongful death lawsuit claims the hospital failed to give Prince proper care after his\"}, {\"start\": 44.34, \"end\": 48.8, \"text\": \"first opioid overdose the week before the fatal incident.\"}, {\"start\": 48.8, \"end\": 57.76, \"text\": \"The suit also names a doctor and various pharmacists at the drugstore.\"}, {\"start\": 57.76, \"end\": 62.8, \"text\": \"Walgreens officials have not commented on the lawsuit.\"}, {\"start\": 62.8, \"end\": 67.4, \"text\": \"The company that operates Trinity Medical Center said they could\"}, {\"start\": 67.4, \"end\": 70.24, \"text\": \"not comment on pending legal matters.\"}, {\"start\": 71.36, \"end\": 78.22, \"text\": \"If you have friends who are really excited about the new Marvel movie, you may not see\"}, {\"start\": 78.22, \"end\": 80.74, \"text\": \"them for a couple of days!\"}, {\"start\": 80.74, \"end\": 89.12, \"text\": \"Beginning early Wednesday afternoon, several theaters across the country are showing 11\"}, {\"start\": 89.12, \"end\": 94.26, \"text\": \"Marvel movies.\"}, {\"start\": 94.42, \"end\": 108.28, \"text\": \"The movie marathon will start with the original \\\"Iron Man\\\" all the way through to \\\"Black Panther,\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 108.48, \"end\": 116.1, \"text\": \"followed by \\\"Infinity War\\\" at 6 PM Thursday.\"}, {\"start\": 116.1, \"end\": 124.52, \"text\": \"That's about 31 hours of Marvel action, all for $75-$100.\"}, {\"start\": 126.38, \"end\": 131.14, \"text\": \"Tennessee state lawmakers honored James Shaw Junior today.\"}, {\"start\": 131.14, \"end\": 148.22, \"text\": \"He is the man who rushed to stop a gunman at a Waffle House.\"}, {\"start\": 148.22, \"end\": 152.719, \"text\": \"The Tennessee House recognize Shaw with the resolution explaining why he is a hero.\"}, {\"start\": 152.72, \"end\": 156.68, \"text\": \"Shaw wrestled an AR-15 from accused gunman Travis Reinking during the attack in Waffle\"}, {\"start\": 156.68, \"end\": 158.38, \"text\": \"House in Antioch on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 158.4, \"end\": 161.92, \"text\": \"A standing ovation erupted in the House after the proclamation.\"}, {\"start\": 161.92, \"end\": 168.84, \"text\": \"Shaw also started a Go-Fund-Me account for the victims' families.\"}, {\"start\": 168.84, \"end\": 173.66, \"text\": \"It went on to raise with $77,000.\"}, {\"start\": 173.66, \"end\": 180.82, \"text\": \"Then someone turned around and started a Go-Fund-Me account for Shaw.\"}, {\"start\": 180.82, \"end\": 185.62, \"text\": \"It raised nearly $50,000 in less than 24 hours.\"}, {\"start\": 187.94, \"end\": 202.54, \"text\": \"Twenty-five-year-old Alek Minassian made his first court appearance in Toronto today.\"}, {\"start\": 202.54, \"end\": 212.96, \"text\": \"He is charged with 10 counts of first-degree murder and 13 counts of attempted murder.\"}, {\"start\": 212.96, \"end\": 219.48, \"text\": \"Authorities say he is the man who used a van to run over multiple people crossing the street\"}, {\"start\": 219.48, \"end\": 222.54, \"text\": \"then drove on the sidewalk to continue his carnage.\"}, {\"start\": 222.54, \"end\": 226.82, \"text\": \"Investigators are still trying to find out why he did it.\"}, {\"start\": 226.82, \"end\": 232.84, \"text\": \"A heavy police presence was seen at Minassian's home as Toronto officials look for those answers.\"}, {\"start\": 234.9, \"end\": 243.08, \"text\": \"We have an update on former President George H.W. Bush.\"}, {\"start\": 243.08, \"end\": 252.22, \"text\": \"He's been in intensive care since the day after his beloved wife, Barbara, was laid\"}, {\"start\": 252.24, \"end\": 254.48, \"text\": \"to rest.\"}, {\"start\": 254.48, \"end\": 261.34, \"text\": \"A family spokesman said the 93-year old was admitted to the Houston Methodist Hospital Sunday\"}, {\"start\": 261.34, \"end\": 269.5, \"text\": \"morning after contracting an infection that spread to his blood.\"}, {\"start\": 269.5, \"end\": 277.44, \"text\": \"But now his condition is stabilized, he is awake, alert and talking.\"}, {\"start\": 277.44, \"end\": 283.28, \"text\": \"According to the spokesman, the 41st president has said he is determined to get healthy and\"}, {\"start\": 283.28, \"end\": 290.76, \"text\": \"return to the family home in Kennebunkport, Maine this summer.\"}, {\"start\": 292.48, \"end\": 305.02, \"text\": \"A team of doctors at John Hopkins Hospital in Baltimore have performed the world's first\"}, {\"start\": 305.02, \"end\": 313.98, \"text\": \"total penile and scrotum transplant.\"}, {\"start\": 313.98, \"end\": 325.74, \"text\": \"A team of nine plastic surgeons and two urological surgeons were involved.\"}, {\"start\": 325.74, \"end\": 329.16, \"text\": \"The 14 hour surgery took place on March 26.\"}, {\"start\": 329.16, \"end\": 340.12, \"text\": \"The recipient was a veteran injured in an IED blast in Afghanistan.\"}, {\"start\": 340.12, \"end\": 349.14, \"text\": \"He has recovered from surgery but wants to remain anonymous.\"}, {\"start\": 349.14, \"end\": 353.94, \"text\": \"He is excited to be released from the hospital this week.\"}, {\"start\": 353.94, \"end\": 363.16, \"text\": \"Doctors say it will take some time for the nerves to grow but they are hopeful he will\"}, {\"start\": 363.16, \"end\": 367.98, \"text\": \"have near-normal urinary and sexual function.\"}, {\"start\": 370.36, \"end\": 372.36, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 372.36, \"end\": 373.92, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 373.92, \"end\": 376.82, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 376.82, \"end\": 382.72, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 382.72, \"end\": 385.04, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 385.04, \"end\": 386.92, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 386.98, \"end\": 390.74, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "Sc8SEW_iaNE": {
    "video_id": "Sc8SEW_iaNE",
    "title": "What is net neutrality? Sign1News Anchor Jethro Wooddall explains in ASL. (American Sign Language)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171215",
    "duration": 159,
    "view_count": 709,
    "description": "What is net neutrality? Sign1News Anchor Jethro Wooddall explains in ASL. (American Sign Language)\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.72, \"end\": 7.92, \"text\": \"Today the Federal Communications Commission voted to repeal the net neutrality rule prohibiting\"}, {\"start\": 7.92, \"end\": 21.68, \"text\": \"internet security providers from prioritizing online content.\"}, {\"start\": 21.68, \"end\": 33.26, \"text\": \"So what in the world is net neutrality and why are people so passionate about it?\"}, {\"start\": 33.28, \"end\": 35.12, \"text\": \"Here's the explanation:\"}, {\"start\": 35.2, \"end\": 37.6, \"text\": \"The \\\"net\\\" refers to the Internet.\"}, {\"start\": 37.6, \"end\": 42.0, \"text\": \"The \\\"neutrality\\\" part is about keeping the Internet as it is today.\"}, {\"start\": 42.0, \"end\": 49.12, \"text\": \"It is a set of rules that went into effect in 2015 to prevent speed traps on the Internet.\"}, {\"start\": 49.12, \"end\": 57.52, \"text\": \"In other words speeding up access to some sites, slowing down access to others or\"}, {\"start\": 57.52, \"end\": 60.76, \"text\": \"blocking certain sites entirely.\"}, {\"start\": 60.76, \"end\": 74.16, \"text\": \"The companies that deliver your Internet like Comcast, Verizon and AT&amp;T have spent millions\"}, {\"start\": 74.16, \"end\": 78.08, \"text\": \"to get rid of net neutrality.\"}, {\"start\": 78.08, \"end\": 83.92, \"text\": \"They argue that having the government micromanage the business\"}, {\"start\": 83.92, \"end\": 88.24, \"text\": \"is not good for them or their consumers.\"}, {\"start\": 88.24, \"end\": 96.16, \"text\": \"On the other side are Internet giants like Facebook and Google,\"}, {\"start\": 96.32, \"end\": 103.76, \"text\": \"streaming services like Netflix and President Obama.\"}, {\"start\": 103.84, \"end\": 110.96, \"text\": \"They all argue the Internet is a public good and should be regulated like one.\"}, {\"start\": 110.96, \"end\": 119.6, \"text\": \"They also say the companies that own Internet pipelines could play favorites.\"}, {\"start\": 119.6, \"end\": 124.96, \"text\": \"For example a content provider like Netflix is in direct competition with Comcast, which\"}, {\"start\": 125.04, \"end\": 136.88, \"text\": \"owns NBC Universal and controls access to the Internet for over 20 million customers.\"}, {\"start\": 136.96, \"end\": 141.68, \"text\": \"You can imagine a scenario where NBC would want to speed up streams to its shows\"}, {\"start\": 141.92, \"end\": 145.44, \"text\": \"and slowdown streams to its rival Netflix.\"}, {\"start\": 145.44, \"end\": 151.0, \"text\": \"But Netflix can afford to pay for fast Internet service.\"}, {\"start\": 151.04, \"end\": 154.82, \"text\": \"It's worth more than $70 billion.\"}, {\"start\": 154.86, \"end\": 159.04, \"text\": \"The tiny startup company cannot.\"}]"
  },
  "Rn1xa9cPbSo": {
    "video_id": "Rn1xa9cPbSo",
    "title": "5.1.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180502",
    "duration": 566,
    "view_count": 1215,
    "description": "5.1.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-The Royal Wedding: An exclusive look inside chapel\n-Immigration processing has begun at the border  \n-May Day: Peaceful rallies and violent clashes\n-Facebook Adds \"clear history\" option\n-Reward offered after deer shot with arrows\n-Illnesses from tick, mosquito and flea bites triple in U.S.\n-Oreo has 3 new flavors, you decide what to keep\n-4th grade boys fight for bathroom privacy\n\nTHE SIGN1",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.32, \"end\": 8.46, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.46, \"end\": 10.78, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.78, \"end\": 12.32, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.32, \"end\": 15.22, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.62, \"end\": 28.96, \"text\": \"The Royal wedding of Prince Harry and American Meghan Markle is less than three weeks away.\"}, {\"start\": 28.96, \"end\": 40.84, \"text\": \"CNN has provided an exclusive look inside Windsor Castle where they will tie the knot.\"}, {\"start\": 40.84, \"end\": 49.62, \"text\": \"The couple will exchange vows inside St. George's Chapel.\"}, {\"start\": 49.62, \"end\": 57.02, \"text\": \"When Markle arrives, she will walk up about 20 steps to the chapel doors.\"}, {\"start\": 57.02, \"end\": 65.8, \"text\": \"She will enter beneath stained-glass windows where about 600 guests will witness the Royal event.\"}, {\"start\": 65.8, \"end\": 74.16, \"text\": \"Markle will walk over toward her fiance and with the words \\\"I do\\\" she will become British royalty.\"}, {\"start\": 74.24, \"end\": 80.32, \"text\": \"Following the nuptials, the newlyweds will leave Windsor Castle in a carriage for a procession\"}, {\"start\": 80.32, \"end\": 82.96, \"text\": \"through the town of Windsor.\"}, {\"start\": 82.96, \"end\": 91.68, \"text\": \"The Queen will host a reception for the couple on the castle grounds and Harry's father Prince\"}, {\"start\": 91.68, \"end\": 99.04, \"text\": \"Charles will host a small reception in the evening with about 200 friends and family.\"}, {\"start\": 100.72, \"end\": 111.98, \"text\": \"US Customs and Border Protection officials have started processing the caravan of migrants\"}, {\"start\": 111.98, \"end\": 115.36, \"text\": \"that arrived from Central America this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 115.36, \"end\": 122.66, \"text\": \"Hundreds of migrants are huddled in tents waiting for their chance to speak with a US\"}, {\"start\": 122.66, \"end\": 130.24, \"text\": \"official and plead their case for being granted asylum in the US.\"}, {\"start\": 130.24, \"end\": 134.78, \"text\": \"We've learned that the people who got in first were selected by their peers to go ahead of\"}, {\"start\": 134.8, \"end\": 137.68, \"text\": \"them, mostly women and children.\"}, {\"start\": 137.68, \"end\": 144.4, \"text\": \"The rest could be there for days or even weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 144.4, \"end\": 152.96, \"text\": \"And if history is an indicator, the odds of the migrants getting asylum are slim.\"}, {\"start\": 152.96, \"end\": 163.42, \"text\": \"Records show between 2011 and 2016, more than 75% of applicants from Honduras, Guatemala\"}, {\"start\": 163.42, \"end\": 167.56, \"text\": \"and El Salvador were rejected.\"}, {\"start\": 167.56, \"end\": 172.82, \"text\": \"But the migrants say they've come too far to turn around.\"}, {\"start\": 172.82, \"end\": 175.28, \"text\": \"They are willing to take their chances.\"}, {\"start\": 177.48, \"end\": 185.78, \"text\": \"May Day marches took place all over the world today.\"}, {\"start\": 185.78, \"end\": 191.1, \"text\": \"It is a day where workers from all sectors gathered to demand better pay and improved\"}, {\"start\": 191.1, \"end\": 194.32, \"text\": \"working conditions.\"}, {\"start\": 194.32, \"end\": 199.3, \"text\": \"Most of the marches were peaceful and organized.\"}, {\"start\": 199.3, \"end\": 204.88, \"text\": \"But protests turned violent in Paris.\"}, {\"start\": 204.88, \"end\": 213.56, \"text\": \"Protesters burned cars, smashed windows, set off road flares and scribbled graffitti on\"}, {\"start\": 213.56, \"end\": 215.56, \"text\": \"buildings.\"}, {\"start\": 215.56, \"end\": 223.24, \"text\": \"Police showed up in riot gear and driving heavy vehicles to restore order.\"}, {\"start\": 223.24, \"end\": 226.2, \"text\": \"No word on if there were any arrests.\"}, {\"start\": 228.52, \"end\": 242.78, \"text\": \"Today Facebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg announced the company is adding a new privacy feature.\"}, {\"start\": 242.78, \"end\": 249.34, \"text\": \"The feature lets you clear your browsing history.\"}, {\"start\": 249.34, \"end\": 254.34, \"text\": \"That includes what you've clicked on and which websites you've gone to.\"}, {\"start\": 254.34, \"end\": 261.32, \"text\": \"Facebook has not laid out exactly when the feature will be available but the company\"}, {\"start\": 261.32, \"end\": 264.28, \"text\": \"says it would take a few months to build it.\"}, {\"start\": 264.28, \"end\": 271.34, \"text\": \"This announcement comes after Zuckerberg's testimony on Capitol Hill last month about\"}, {\"start\": 271.34, \"end\": 283.76, \"text\": \"Facebook allowing a political data firm to improperly access data from 87 million users.\"}, {\"start\": 285.9, \"end\": 291.48, \"text\": \"An investigation is underway in Southwest Oregon after several living deer were found\"}, {\"start\": 291.6, \"end\": 295.7, \"text\": \"shot with arrows.\"}, {\"start\": 295.7, \"end\": 303.92, \"text\": \"Oregon State police posted these photos on their Facebook page Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 303.92, \"end\": 311.32, \"text\": \"The pictures show deer, walking through a field with arrows shot from their bodies.\"}, {\"start\": 311.32, \"end\": 316.92, \"text\": \"Officials say that they are able to eat and walk and their injuries don't appear to be\"}, {\"start\": 316.92, \"end\": 320.82, \"text\": \"life-threatening.\"}, {\"start\": 320.82, \"end\": 334.24, \"text\": \"The Oregon Hunters Association is offering a $2,600 reward for information leading to\"}, {\"start\": 334.24, \"end\": 336.42, \"text\": \"an arrest.\"}, {\"start\": 338.54, \"end\": 349.44, \"text\": \"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention is warning people to beware of bugs!\"}, {\"start\": 349.44, \"end\": 358.06, \"text\": \"According to a new CDC report, illnesses from mosquitoes, ticks and flea bites tripled in\"}, {\"start\": 358.06, \"end\": 362.84, \"text\": \"the US from 2004 to 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 362.84, \"end\": 369.24, \"text\": \"The report says more than 642,000 cases of diseases from the bugs were reported during\"}, {\"start\": 369.24, \"end\": 371.06, \"text\": \"that period.\"}, {\"start\": 371.06, \"end\": 385.22, \"text\": \"The illnesses include Lyme disease, West Nile virus, Zika virus, Dengue fever and plague.\"}, {\"start\": 385.22, \"end\": 392.14, \"text\": \"Tick-borne diseases accounted for more than 75% of the cases.\"}, {\"start\": 392.14, \"end\": 399.5, \"text\": \"And health experts found at least nine diseases were newly discovered or introduced into the\"}, {\"start\": 399.5, \"end\": 400.82, \"text\": \"US since 2004.\"}, {\"start\": 400.82, \"end\": 404.32, \"text\": \"The study did not go into the reasons behind the increase.\"}, {\"start\": 404.32, \"end\": 411.3, \"text\": \"But CDC officials say people should take precautions to prevent bites.\"}, {\"start\": 413.68, \"end\": 425.72, \"text\": \"Nabisco has introduced three new limited-edition Oreo flavors.\"}, {\"start\": 425.72, \"end\": 436.56, \"text\": \"The company says it received hundreds of thousands of ideas for new flavors and three finalists\"}, {\"start\": 436.56, \"end\": 445.12, \"text\": \"were chosen after being judged on taste appeal, creativity and originality.\"}, {\"start\": 445.12, \"end\": 454.14, \"text\": \"The flavors are cherry cola, kettle corn and pina colada.\"}, {\"start\": 454.14, \"end\": 458.66, \"text\": \"Now Nabisco is trying to pick a winner and they need your help.\"}, {\"start\": 458.66, \"end\": 467.34, \"text\": \"The company is hosting a contest to determine the public's favorite.\"}, {\"start\": 467.34, \"end\": 470.26, \"text\": \"So go ahead and start snacking!\"}, {\"start\": 470.26, \"end\": 478.18, \"text\": \"After sampling each one, go to www.myOreocreation.com\"}, {\"start\": 478.18, \"end\": 480.74, \"text\": \"to cast your vote for your favorite.\"}, {\"start\": 480.74, \"end\": 484.54, \"text\": \"We'll let you know which one wins.\"}, {\"start\": 486.0, \"end\": 494.78, \"text\": \"A group of Utah fourth grade boys are learning how to make their voices heard.\"}, {\"start\": 494.78, \"end\": 501.52, \"text\": \"They say it's uncomfortable to have other kids looking at them while they're using the\"}, {\"start\": 501.52, \"end\": 505.219, \"text\": \"bathroom so they're fighting for more privacy.\"}, {\"start\": 505.22, \"end\": 513.68, \"text\": \"Their goal is to get partitions installed between the urinals at all district schools.\"}, {\"start\": 513.68, \"end\": 522.78, \"text\": \"After learning about civil rights and petitions, the boys began their own, collecting over\"}, {\"start\": 522.78, \"end\": 524.66, \"text\": \"150 signatures.\"}, {\"start\": 524.66, \"end\": 528.32, \"text\": \"Then they appeared before the school board to argue their case.\"}, {\"start\": 528.32, \"end\": 534.58, \"text\": \"Administrators say they are now looking at solutions to the student's concerns.\"}, {\"start\": 537.44, \"end\": 539.62, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 539.84, \"end\": 541.38, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 541.38, \"end\": 543.96, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 543.96, \"end\": 549.22, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 549.22, \"end\": 551.6, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 551.6, \"end\": 553.0, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 553.0, \"end\": 556.84, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "2WvGsW3j3tI": {
    "video_id": "2WvGsW3j3tI",
    "title": "Tiger cub found in express mail container (ASL - 2.7.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180208",
    "duration": 60,
    "view_count": 64,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.04, \"end\": 9.84, \"text\": \"Mexican authorities say they rescued a two-month-old Bengal tiger cub from a package intended for\"}, {\"start\": 9.84, \"end\": 14.98, \"text\": \"shipping.\"}, {\"start\": 14.98, \"end\": 24.5, \"text\": \"Officials reportedly heard noises and called in sniffing dogs, who confirmed something\"}, {\"start\": 24.5, \"end\": 27.56, \"text\": \"was alive inside the box.\"}, {\"start\": 27.56, \"end\": 39.34, \"text\": \"Authorities say the cub was completely sedated and had no food or water.\"}, {\"start\": 39.34, \"end\": 49.3, \"text\": \"Bengal tigers are considered endangered.\"}, {\"start\": 49.3, \"end\": 59.02, \"text\": \"The cub is now in the custody of Mexico's Department of Natural Resources and Environment.\"}]"
  },
  "9d_BaaU3GUo": {
    "video_id": "9d_BaaU3GUo",
    "title": "What's in your Starbucks coffee mug?",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20181025",
    "duration": 98,
    "view_count": 433,
    "description": "Pictured: Howard Rosenblum, President, National Association of the Deaf\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.16, \"end\": 11.94, \"text\": \"As you know earlier this week our Sign1News crew was allowed a sneak peek into the new\"}, {\"start\": 11.94, \"end\": 14.94, \"text\": \"Starbucks signing store in Washington, DC.\"}, {\"start\": 14.94, \"end\": 25.34, \"text\": \"Thanks to you that video has gone viral, with over 640,000 views and 13,000 shares.\"}, {\"start\": 25.34, \"end\": 30.42, \"text\": \"We also noticed from your comments that many of you are interested in getting your hands\"}, {\"start\": 30.42, \"end\": 33.24, \"text\": \"on the Starbucks signing store coffee mug.\"}, {\"start\": 33.24, \"end\": 36.22, \"text\": \"We want to know what you would put in the mug.\"}, {\"start\": 36.22, \"end\": 42.86, \"text\": \"What's your favorite Starbucks drink?\"}, {\"start\": 42.86, \"end\": 50.28, \"text\": \"My favorite is white chocolate mocha frappe.\"}, {\"start\": 50.28, \"end\": 56.18, \"text\": \"While we were in Washington, DC we asked some of the people in the signing store what their\"}, {\"start\": 56.18, \"end\": 59.51, \"text\": \"favorite Starbucks drink is.\"}, {\"start\": 59.51, \"end\": 61.84, \"text\": \"Here's what they had to say.\"}, {\"start\": 61.9, \"end\": 65.54, \"text\": \"My favorite is white chocolate mocha.\"}, {\"start\": 65.54, \"end\": 74.94, \"text\": \"I love a latte with almond milk and three pumps of vanilla.\"}, {\"start\": 74.94, \"end\": 81.3, \"text\": \"My favorite is a carmel macchiato.\"}, {\"start\": 81.3, \"end\": 87.64, \"text\": \"My favorite coffee is cold brew.\"}, {\"start\": 87.64, \"end\": 92.8, \"text\": \"My favorite is iced carmel macchiato.\"}, {\"start\": 92.8, \"end\": 94.34, \"text\": \"No coffee for me.\"}, {\"start\": 94.34, \"end\": 98.28, \"text\": \"I favorite is black iced tea.\"}]"
  },
  "9-UyXaEh7UI": {
    "video_id": "9-UyXaEh7UI",
    "title": "Severe storms across Midwest, South (ASL - 2.25.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180226",
    "duration": 62,
    "view_count": 96,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.7, \"end\": 3.46, \"text\": \"According to the National Weather Service, several people in Kentucky were killed due\"}, {\"start\": 3.46, \"end\": 5.66, \"text\": \"to severe storms.\"}, {\"start\": 5.66, \"end\": 12.559, \"text\": \"The storm brought relentless rain, fierce winds and lots of damage.\"}, {\"start\": 12.56, \"end\": 18.46, \"text\": \"Most of the damage happened late Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 18.46, \"end\": 24.52, \"text\": \"Residents they when they looked outside and saw trees bowing they knew they had to go\"}, {\"start\": 24.52, \"end\": 27.46, \"text\": \"seek shelter.\"}, {\"start\": 27.46, \"end\": 32.72, \"text\": \"Parts of the state also dealt with massive flooding.\"}, {\"start\": 32.72, \"end\": 40.62, \"text\": \"And in some areas of Tennessee the storm ripped through home after home, destroy nearly everything\"}, {\"start\": 40.62, \"end\": 42.8, \"text\": \"in sight.\"}, {\"start\": 42.8, \"end\": 49.84, \"text\": \"In Ohio heavy rain led to widespread flooding.\"}, {\"start\": 49.84, \"end\": 56.0, \"text\": \"Even parts of Arkansas witnessed the devastation.\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 59.86, \"text\": \"At least one storm-related death has been confirmed there.\"}]"
  },
  "bnKRNLYxhA8": {
    "video_id": "bnKRNLYxhA8",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.2.18: News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180203",
    "duration": 543,
    "view_count": 1759,
    "description": "2.2.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Father of abused girls tries to attack Nassar\n-Trump approves release of controversial memo\n-CDC report: flu deaths rising\n-Fidel Castro’s eldest son commits suicide\n-Officer makes heroic save\n-Game day food safety tips\n-Groundhog Day! 6 more weeks of winter\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in Ameri",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.04, \"end\": 7.68, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.68, \"end\": 10.0, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.04, \"end\": 11.12, \"text\": \"I’m Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 11.2, \"end\": 13.52, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.44, \"end\": 21.76, \"text\": \"Chaos erupted in a Michigan courtroom today.\"}, {\"start\": 21.76, \"end\": 33.32, \"text\": \"During the sentencing hearing for former sports physician Larry Nassar, the father of three\"}, {\"start\": 33.32, \"end\": 36.96, \"text\": \"daughters sexually abused by Nassar tried to attack him.\"}, {\"start\": 36.96, \"end\": 44.88, \"text\": \"Randall Margraves stood next to two of his daughters as they gave impact statements against\"}, {\"start\": 44.88, \"end\": 48.32, \"text\": \"Nassar.\"}, {\"start\": 48.32, \"end\": 52.92, \"text\": \"When they finished speaking, Margraves asked the judge if she would give him just five\"}, {\"start\": 52.92, \"end\": 59.28, \"text\": \"minutes alone in a locked room with “this demon.”\"}, {\"start\": 59.36, \"end\": 61.6, \"text\": \"The judge said “No.\"}, {\"start\": 61.6, \"end\": 65.32, \"text\": \"That’s not how the legal system works.”\"}, {\"start\": 65.32, \"end\": 69.16, \"text\": \"That’s when the father went after Nassar.\"}, {\"start\": 69.16, \"end\": 75.68, \"text\": \"He was tackled and arrested by security before reaching Nassar.\"}, {\"start\": 75.68, \"end\": 76.88, \"text\": \"Here's the video.\"}, {\"start\": 96.96, \"end\": 105.44, \"text\": \"After a brief recess, Margraves return to court and apologized for his actions.\"}, {\"start\": 105.6, \"end\": 108.32, \"text\": \"He was released without punishment.\"}, {\"start\": 110.4, \"end\": 120.24, \"text\": \"Today President Trump authorized the release of a controversial Republican memo.\"}, {\"start\": 120.4, \"end\": 126.0, \"text\": \"It’s a report from the House Intelligence Committee compiled by Republican Congressman\"}, {\"start\": 126.0, \"end\": 128.12, \"text\": \"Devin Nunes.\"}, {\"start\": 128.12, \"end\": 138.2, \"text\": \"The report accuses the FBI for abusing surveillance powers and accuses the Democrats of being\"}, {\"start\": 138.36, \"end\": 141.56, \"text\": \"behind the Russia investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 141.56, \"end\": 152.0, \"text\": \"The memo was released over objections from the Justice Department and the FBI.\"}, {\"start\": 152.08, \"end\": 158.92, \"text\": \"Both agencies had serious concerns about the document’s accuracy.\"}, {\"start\": 158.92, \"end\": 170.24, \"text\": \"Trump calls the memo a disgrace and sources say he sees it as a way to discredit the entire\"}, {\"start\": 170.24, \"end\": 173.64, \"text\": \"Russia investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 173.64, \"end\": 181.04, \"text\": \"For now, the president refuses to say whether he will fire the top Justice Department official\"}, {\"start\": 181.04, \"end\": 184.52, \"text\": \"overseeing the investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 186.28, \"end\": 193.6, \"text\": \"Officials with the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) say flu hospitalizations\"}, {\"start\": 193.92, \"end\": 201.52, \"text\": \"and deaths are on the rise because of a particularly rough flu season.\"}, {\"start\": 201.92, \"end\": 211.28, \"text\": \"On Friday the agency reported 16 more children have died because of the flu, bringing the\"}, {\"start\": 211.28, \"end\": 213.56, \"text\": \"total number killed by the virus to 53.\"}, {\"start\": 213.56, \"end\": 220.28, \"text\": \"Forty-eight states are reporting widespread flu activity.\"}, {\"start\": 220.44, \"end\": 228.2, \"text\": \"And a CDC spokesperson says the wave of flu cases hasn’t peaked yet.\"}, {\"start\": 229.84, \"end\": 240.28, \"text\": \"Cuban state media says Fidel Castro’s eldest son, Fidel Castro Diaz Balart, committed suicide\"}, {\"start\": 240.36, \"end\": 243.36, \"text\": \"Thursday.\"}, {\"start\": 243.36, \"end\": 248.96, \"text\": \"He was also known as “Fidelito” or “Little Fidel.”\"}, {\"start\": 249.28, \"end\": 253.24, \"text\": \"He was 68 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 253.24, \"end\": 259.76, \"text\": \"Doctors say he had been receiving treatment for depression for several months.\"}, {\"start\": 259.76, \"end\": 270.72, \"text\": \"Castro Diaz-Balart was the only son of Castro and Mirta Diaz-Balart.\"}, {\"start\": 270.88, \"end\": 278.16, \"text\": \"Fidel Castro also had six other sons and two daughters.\"}, {\"start\": 279.84, \"end\": 293.28, \"text\": \"An Illinois deputy is being called a hero after he saved himself and three others from\"}, {\"start\": 293.28, \"end\": 296.44, \"text\": \"an alleged drunk driver.\"}, {\"start\": 296.44, \"end\": 308.6, \"text\": \"The officer was conducting a DUI stop when another vehicle sped past and nearly hit them.\"}, {\"start\": 308.68, \"end\": 312.36, \"text\": \"The officer shoved the others out of the way just in the nick of time.\"}, {\"start\": 312.36, \"end\": 314.08, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 326.08, \"end\": 334.16, \"text\": \"After the car passed, the officer ran back to his car, chased down the vehicle and arrested\"}, {\"start\": 334.16, \"end\": 337.44, \"text\": \"that driver for DUI.\"}, {\"start\": 339.36, \"end\": 347.92, \"text\": \"Super Bowl Sunday is a time for fun, food, friends and football.\"}, {\"start\": 347.92, \"end\": 353.84, \"text\": \"But those parties can also be full of germs.\"}, {\"start\": 354.16, \"end\": 361.84, \"text\": \"Here are some tips to make sure your Super Bowl party is a healthy one, starting with\"}, {\"start\": 362.0, \"end\": 365.92, \"text\": \"the buffet table.\"}, {\"start\": 366.24, \"end\": 374.64, \"text\": \"Make sure it’s clean and not contaminated with old food that could contain bacteria.\"}, {\"start\": 374.64, \"end\": 379.68, \"text\": \"Wash your hands and cutting boards.\"}, {\"start\": 379.68, \"end\": 389.76, \"text\": \"Keep foods like raw chicken, hamburger meat and hotdogs away from one another to avoid\"}, {\"start\": 389.92, \"end\": 395.04, \"text\": \"cross contamination.\"}, {\"start\": 395.04, \"end\": 401.44, \"text\": \"And cook everything well.\"}, {\"start\": 401.44, \"end\": 411.04, \"text\": \"Make sure chicken wings reach a minimum internal temperature of 165 degrees and ground beef\"}, {\"start\": 411.2, \"end\": 414.48, \"text\": \"items reach 160 degrees.\"}, {\"start\": 414.48, \"end\": 418.72, \"text\": \"And keep cold foods cool.\"}, {\"start\": 418.72, \"end\": 430.32, \"text\": \"Use small serving trays or bowls of ice to keep salsa, mayonnaise and guacamole around\"}, {\"start\": 430.32, \"end\": 432.96, \"text\": \"40 degrees or colder.\"}, {\"start\": 434.24, \"end\": 439.92, \"text\": \"If you were hoping to put your winter clothes\"}, {\"start\": 439.92, \"end\": 443.28, \"text\": \"away for the season, sorry no such luck.\"}, {\"start\": 443.28, \"end\": 454.6, \"text\": \"The famous groundhog Punxsutawney Phil made his annual prediction Friday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 454.6, \"end\": 461.64, \"text\": \"According to the 100 year old tradition, if Phil emerges from his hole and does not see\"}, {\"start\": 461.64, \"end\": 467.54, \"text\": \"his shadow, spring comes early.\"}, {\"start\": 467.54, \"end\": 477.26, \"text\": \"If he does see his shadow, that means six more weeks of winter.\"}, {\"start\": 477.34, \"end\": 487.28, \"text\": \"Unfortunately, Phil saw his shadow.\"}, {\"start\": 487.28, \"end\": 490.84, \"text\": \"But it’s all in good fun.\"}, {\"start\": 490.84, \"end\": 500.02, \"text\": \"Groundhog’s Day is tied to when groundhogs typically wake up from hibernation.\"}, {\"start\": 500.02, \"end\": 511.58, \"text\": \"The National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) says the groundhog has no weather predictive\"}, {\"start\": 511.58, \"end\": 513.94, \"text\": \"skills whatsoever.\"}, {\"start\": 515.9, \"end\": 518.88, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 518.88, \"end\": 521.16, \"text\": \"I’m Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 521.16, \"end\": 523.82, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 523.82, \"end\": 529.04, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 529.04, \"end\": 535.56, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "5CQ9N0ls0Hc": {
    "video_id": "5CQ9N0ls0Hc",
    "title": "Tillerson aide fired (ASL - 3.13.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180314",
    "duration": 34,
    "view_count": 67,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.38, \"end\": 7.56, \"text\": \"Hours after Tillerson was let go, the White House also got rid of Tillerson's aide Steve\"}, {\"start\": 7.6, \"end\": 11.4, \"text\": \"Goldstein.\"}, {\"start\": 11.4, \"end\": 15.98, \"text\": \"He was fired after he publicly contradicted the White House's account of Tillerson's firing.\"}, {\"start\": 15.98, \"end\": 23.12, \"text\": \"Goldstein sent out a tweet that said Tillerson never spoke to the president and found out\"}, {\"start\": 23.16, \"end\": 25.76, \"text\": \"he was fired on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 25.76, \"end\": 31.6, \"text\": \"Asked Tuesday how Tillerson learned of his dismissal, Trump didn't directly answer the\"}, {\"start\": 31.88, \"end\": 33.44, \"text\": \"question.\"}]"
  },
  "fldFnr1xG2g": {
    "video_id": "fldFnr1xG2g",
    "title": "1st case of super-resistant gonorrhea reported (ASL - 3.29.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180330",
    "duration": 53,
    "view_count": 389,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.68, \"end\": 9.6, \"text\": \"The first case of super-resistant gonorrhea has been reported in the United Kingdom.\"}, {\"start\": 9.66, \"end\": 14.58, \"text\": \"Health officials say a man is infected with a form of gonorrhea that is completely resistant\"}, {\"start\": 14.58, \"end\": 16.5, \"text\": \"to treatment.\"}, {\"start\": 16.5, \"end\": 26.62, \"text\": \"The man caught the sexually transmitted disease in southeast Asia one month before his symptoms\"}, {\"start\": 26.62, \"end\": 30.0, \"text\": \"began.\"}, {\"start\": 30.0, \"end\": 45.02, \"text\": \"Officials say the man is being treated intravenously with the antibiotic Ertapenem.\"}, {\"start\": 45.02, \"end\": 47.46, \"text\": \"It appears to be effective for now.\"}, {\"start\": 47.46, \"end\": 52.96, \"text\": \"The man will be tested again in April.\"}]"
  },
  "EnUyoD85HKU": {
    "video_id": "EnUyoD85HKU",
    "title": "Lonely Bolivian water frog seeks mate on Match.com (ASL - 2.13.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180214",
    "duration": 49,
    "view_count": 210,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.14, \"end\": 9.5, \"text\": \"A frog named Romeo is looking for a mate on Match.com!\"}, {\"start\": 9.5, \"end\": 20.84, \"text\": \"The 11-year-old Bolivian water frog is trying to save his species.\"}, {\"start\": 20.84, \"end\": 29.38, \"text\": \"Researchers say Romeo has been looking for mate for the past decade with no luck.\"}, {\"start\": 29.38, \"end\": 36.82, \"text\": \"So Match.com has started a fund raising campaign to help Romeo find a mate.\"}, {\"start\": 36.82, \"end\": 44.32, \"text\": \"The goal is to raise 15-thousand dollars before Valentine's Day for 10 trips to places where\"}, {\"start\": 44.32, \"end\": 47.92, \"text\": \"Romeo's species was once common.\"}]"
  },
  "EB78MNLokOo": {
    "video_id": "EB78MNLokOo",
    "title": "LADY GAGA REVEALS LAS VEGAS RESIDENCY",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171221",
    "duration": 58,
    "view_count": 65,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.0, \"end\": 15.64, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga now has a residency engagement at the MGM Park theater in Las Vegas.\"}, {\"start\": 15.64, \"end\": 20.86, \"text\": \"The deal was signed over the weekend and the pop star will begin performing next year.\"}, {\"start\": 20.86, \"end\": 30.72, \"text\": \"She will perform 74 days with the possibility of adding more.\"}, {\"start\": 30.72, \"end\": 35.4, \"text\": \"The deal could be worth nearly $100 million.\"}, {\"start\": 35.4, \"end\": 44.76, \"text\": \"According to the Hollywood Reporter, Gaga will get upwards of $1 million per show.\"}, {\"start\": 44.76, \"end\": 54.38, \"text\": \"According to Pollstar, Lady Gaga grossed about $2.5 million per show on her last tour,\"}, {\"start\": 54.38, \"end\": 57.58, \"text\": \"which included 37 dates.\"}]"
  },
  "olpXrUauOTs": {
    "video_id": "olpXrUauOTs",
    "title": "Dr. G answers your question: Can you get coronavirus and the flu at the same time?",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200324",
    "duration": 120,
    "view_count": 331,
    "description": "Posted 3.23.20",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.62, \"end\": 12.08, \"text\": \"Sign1News anchor Candace Jones heard that you can get coronavirus of the flu at\"}, {\"start\": 12.08, \"end\": 13.64, \"text\": \"the same time.\"}, {\"start\": 13.64, \"end\": 16.24, \"text\": \"Is that possible?\"}, {\"start\": 16.24, \"end\": 18.94, \"text\": \"Yes but it doesn't happen often.\"}, {\"start\": 18.94, \"end\": 27.5, \"text\": \"Right now in the US March is flu season and it's almost over.\"}, {\"start\": 27.5, \"end\": 32.92, \"text\": \"So more and more people are getting sick and worried about the coronavirus.\"}, {\"start\": 32.92, \"end\": 37.24, \"text\": \"But if you're sick stop for a moment.\"}, {\"start\": 37.24, \"end\": 40.66, \"text\": \"There is a Yes/No checklist you can go down of what's bothering you.\"}, {\"start\": 40.66, \"end\": 48.16, \"text\": \"Do you have a sore throat, do you have a fever, is my ear aching, am I coughing, is my nose\"}, {\"start\": 48.16, \"end\": 54.7, \"text\": \"running, do I have allergies, are my eyes, ears and throat itching, am I having breathing\"}, {\"start\": 54.7, \"end\": 56.84, \"text\": \"problems?\"}, {\"start\": 56.94, \"end\": 59.88, \"text\": \"Just go down the list and then call the doctor.\"}, {\"start\": 59.88, \"end\": 61.78, \"text\": \"Don't leave your home.\"}, {\"start\": 61.78, \"end\": 67.9, \"text\": \"If you get really sick and you can't breathe, yes go to the hospital or emergency room.\"}, {\"start\": 67.9, \"end\": 75.28, \"text\": \"But if you're okay and just feeling a little sick or you don't feel good, call first.\"}, {\"start\": 75.28, \"end\": 80.74, \"text\": \"The good news right now is that many doctors including myself are seeing their patients\"}, {\"start\": 80.74, \"end\": 83.1, \"text\": \"via videoconference.\"}, {\"start\": 83.1, \"end\": 88.18, \"text\": \"You don't need to go to the doctors office and make other people sick.\"}, {\"start\": 88.4, \"end\": 93.22, \"text\": \"Just wait, go down the checklist, see what's happening, then call and ask.\"}, {\"start\": 93.22, \"end\": 97.14, \"text\": \"Many doctors will give you good information over the phone first.\"}, {\"start\": 97.14, \"end\": 101.64, \"text\": \"Then later, if you need to go, they will help understand where to go.\"}, {\"start\": 101.72, \"end\": 106.3, \"text\": \"And if you do show up at the hospital right now without a doctor's appointment first,\"}, {\"start\": 106.3, \"end\": 109.72, \"text\": \"many hospitals would tell you to go back home and call your doctor.\"}, {\"start\": 109.72, \"end\": 114.46, \"text\": \"And I don't want you to go to the hospital and then have to come all the way back home.\"}, {\"start\": 114.46, \"end\": 115.94, \"text\": \"That's very frustrating.\"}, {\"start\": 115.94, \"end\": 120.44, \"text\": \"First, if it's not an emergency, call the doctor.\"}]"
  },
  "dtxwmtPjHKM": {
    "video_id": "dtxwmtPjHKM",
    "title": "Most Americans can’t cover $1,000 emergency (ASL - 1.19.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180120",
    "duration": 77,
    "view_count": 393,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.1, \"end\": 8.06, \"text\": \"If you were hit with a $1,000 emergency, would you be able to cover it?\"}, {\"start\": 8.06, \"end\": 13.06, \"text\": \"The majority of Americans can't.\"}, {\"start\": 13.1, \"end\": 25.0, \"text\": \"A new report from BankRate.com found that only 39% would be able to pay a bill that\"}, {\"start\": 25.1, \"end\": 29.72, \"text\": \"size out of savings.\"}, {\"start\": 29.72, \"end\": 43.54, \"text\": \"Among those who say they couldn't pay, 36% said they would need to borrow the money or\"}, {\"start\": 43.54, \"end\": 47.64, \"text\": \"put it on a credit card.\"}, {\"start\": 47.64, \"end\": 59.38, \"text\": \"The report also found younger millennials aged 18 to 27 were the most likely of all\"}, {\"start\": 59.38, \"end\": 69.66, \"text\": \"age groups to borrow from family or friends in an emergency situation, while older millennials\"}, {\"start\": 69.66, \"end\": 74.68, \"text\": \"aged 28 to 37 were those most likely to reduce spending on other things.\"}]"
  },
  "bj32_z1O-RI": {
    "video_id": "bj32_z1O-RI",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.25.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171125",
    "duration": 618,
    "view_count": 483,
    "description": "November 25, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-EGYPT STRIKES BACK AFTER DEADLY TERROR ATTACK\n-MOSQUE DEATH TOLL RISES\n-SHOWDOWN OVER CONSUMER AGENCY LEADER\n-TRUMP TIME MAGAZINE MAN OF THE YEAR?\n-IRS BEEFS UP SECURITY TO PROTECT TRUMP'S TAX RETURNS\n-JEFF BEZOS IS NOW WORTH $100 BILLION\n-FIRST DAUGHTERS DEFEND MALIA OBAMA\n-CYBER MONDAY ONLINE SHOPPING SCAMS\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to de",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.68, \"end\": 11.36, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 11.36, \"end\": 14.4, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.46, \"end\": 22.72, \"text\": \"In response to Friday's deadly mosque attack, the Egyptian military released a\"}, {\"start\": 22.74, \"end\": 29.02, \"text\": \"video showing airstrikes performed on Saturday to target terrorists' vehicles\"}, {\"start\": 29.02, \"end\": 33.91, \"text\": \"and outposts in Sinai.  According to a statement posted by the military, Egypt's Air Force tracked down vehicles\"}, {\"start\": 33.91, \"end\": 40.58, \"text\": \"involved in the brutal terrorist attack, killing all terrorists inside those vehicles.\"}, {\"start\": 40.6, \"end\": 46.04, \"text\": \"While no one has claimed responsibility for the terrorist\"}, {\"start\": 46.04, \"end\": 55.54, \"text\": \"attack but experts say northern Sinai is considered Isis turf.\"}, {\"start\": 57.58, \"end\": 64.78, \"text\": \"The death toll in the mosque attack in Egypt has risen to\"}, {\"start\": 64.82, \"end\": 70.32, \"text\": \"305 people killed -- with 27 children among the dead.\"}, {\"start\": 70.32, \"end\": 79.34, \"text\": \"Witnesses say the deadly attacks started with an improvised explosive device going off.\"}, {\"start\": 79.34, \"end\": 90.06, \"text\": \"When worshipers came outside, 25 to 30 gunmen were waiting with guns\"}, {\"start\": 90.06, \"end\": 92.24, \"text\": \"and fired at them.\"}, {\"start\": 92.24, \"end\": 99.52, \"text\": \"One witness said when worshipers stopped fleeing the mosque the gunmen went inside\"}, {\"start\": 99.64, \"end\": 105.6, \"text\": \"to continue their rampage.\"}, {\"start\": 105.6, \"end\": 113.24, \"text\": \"Witnesses also reported seeing gunmen firing on ambulances.\"}, {\"start\": 114.88, \"end\": 118.56, \"text\": \"There is a lot of confusion this morning over who is leading the Consumer\"}, {\"start\": 118.56, \"end\": 133.36, \"text\": \"Financial Protection Bureau or CFPB.\"}, {\"start\": 133.4, \"end\": 140.06, \"text\": \"CFPB is the agency that aims to help safeguard your finances.\"}, {\"start\": 140.1, \"end\": 154.32, \"text\": \"It was created after the 2008 financial crisis to protect consumers and keep an eye on Wall Street.\"}, {\"start\": 154.34, \"end\": 157.54, \"text\": \"But at the moment it doesn't have a clear leader.\"}, {\"start\": 157.54, \"end\": 159.36, \"text\": \"Here's why:\"}, {\"start\": 159.36, \"end\": 175.52, \"text\": \"President Trump tapped White House budget director Mick Mulvaney to be interim chief of the agency.\"}, {\"start\": 175.52, \"end\": 186.58, \"text\": \"But that announcement came just hours after director Richard Cordray\"}, {\"start\": 186.58, \"end\": 196.56, \"text\": \"resigned and named his chief of staff Leandra English as his successor.\"}, {\"start\": 196.56, \"end\": 203.36, \"text\": \"The appointment of two officials to the same post sets up a political and legal clash.\"}, {\"start\": 203.36, \"end\": 211.28, \"text\": \"President Trump will ultimately nominate\"}, {\"start\": 211.28, \"end\": 215.64, \"text\": \"a permanent director but that could take months.\"}, {\"start\": 215.64, \"end\": 217.34, \"text\": \"Up until that time, there's still the big question:\"}, {\"start\": 217.34, \"end\": 225.32, \"text\": \"Who's in charge when CFPB employees return to work on Monday?\"}, {\"start\": 227.48, \"end\": 237.32, \"text\": \"It looks like President Trump will not be TIME magazine's Person of the Year for 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 237.32, \"end\": 243.84, \"text\": \"The president said on Twitter Friday that he turned down a potential offer to the title.\"}, {\"start\": 243.84, \"end\": 249.74, \"text\": \"In his tweet Trump said the magazine told him he would\"}, {\"start\": 249.74, \"end\": 255.34, \"text\": \"probably be given the honor but he would have to do an interview and a photo shoot.\"}, {\"start\": 255.34, \"end\": 256.92, \"text\": \"He said he passed on the idea.\"}, {\"start\": 256.96, \"end\": 263.88, \"text\": \"The magazine refuted Trump's claims in a statement.\"}, {\"start\": 263.94, \"end\": 276.32, \"text\": \"The president was named TIME's Person of the Year in 2016 following his victory in the 2016 election.\"}, {\"start\": 278.64, \"end\": 284.08, \"text\": \"President Trump bucked tradition when he decided not to release his tax returns\"}, {\"start\": 284.08, \"end\": 289.04, \"text\": \"to the public. And now the IRS is going to unprecedented lengths to make sure\"}, {\"start\": 289.12, \"end\": 296.04, \"text\": \"they don't end up in the wrong hands and in the public eye.\"}, {\"start\": 296.04, \"end\": 303.74, \"text\": \"The agency locked down Trump's digital returns in 2016\"}, {\"start\": 303.74, \"end\": 312.32, \"text\": \"and is now focusing on the physical documents.\"}, {\"start\": 312.34, \"end\": 318.56, \"text\": \"One hacking magazine has offered $10,000 to anyone\"}, {\"start\": 318.56, \"end\": 326.78, \"text\": \"who can obtain a copy of the president's paperwork.\"}, {\"start\": 326.8, \"end\": 335.42, \"text\": \"Last year WikiLeaks tweeted a request.\"}, {\"start\": 335.5, \"end\": 340.284, \"text\": \"In March MSNBC got a few pages from a\"}, {\"start\": 340.284, \"end\": 346.62, \"text\": \"journalist who said he found them in his mailbox.\"}, {\"start\": 346.7, \"end\": 352.6, \"text\": \"One private investigator is currently facing federal charges after\"}, {\"start\": 352.64, \"end\": 356.7, \"text\": \"allegedly guessing a social security number and attempting to use it to\"}, {\"start\": 356.72, \"end\": 359.5, \"text\": \"access the president's tax information.\"}, {\"start\": 361.48, \"end\": 369.38, \"text\": \"Amazon founder Jeff Bezos is now worth a\"}, {\"start\": 369.38, \"end\": 373.68, \"text\": \"whopping 100 billion dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 373.7, \"end\": 377.9, \"text\": \"That's according to Bloomberg, a service that\"}, {\"start\": 377.9, \"end\": 383.32, \"text\": \"tracks the real-time net worth of the world's richest people.\"}, {\"start\": 383.32, \"end\": 392.94, \"text\": \"The other service, Forbes, has him at just a tad less at ninety nine point six billion dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 392.96, \"end\": 408.02, \"text\": \"Bezos reached a hundred billion dollars Friday thanks to a rise in Amazon stock.\"}, {\"start\": 408.02, \"end\": 414.26, \"text\": \"Amazon stock climbed after reports showed online shopping for Thanksgiving\"}, {\"start\": 414.26, \"end\": 420.08, \"text\": \"and Black Friday jumping 18 percent over last year.\"}, {\"start\": 420.08, \"end\": 427.78, \"text\": \"It's believed Bill Gates, the co-founder of Microsoft, is the only other person\"}, {\"start\": 427.78, \"end\": 432.96, \"text\": \"ever to have reached the 1 billion dollar mark.\"}, {\"start\": 435.08, \"end\": 445.98, \"text\": \"FIrst daughters Chelsea Clinton and Ivanka Trump are\"}, {\"start\": 445.98, \"end\": 450.54, \"text\": \"defending Malia Obama.\"}, {\"start\": 450.54, \"end\": 453.7, \"text\": \"Video has circulated of what appears to be Malia\"}, {\"start\": 453.7, \"end\": 458.64, \"text\": \"blowing smoke rings in a bathroom.\"}, {\"start\": 458.64, \"end\": 464.02, \"text\": \"This past weekend Malia was photographed kissing a\"}, {\"start\": 464.02, \"end\": 471.18, \"text\": \"boy at a tailgate party before a football game.\"}, {\"start\": 471.18, \"end\": 478.94, \"text\": \"Chelsea Clinton tweeted this:\"}, {\"start\": 478.94, \"end\": 487.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Malia Obama's private life, as a young woman, a college student, a private\"}, {\"start\": 487.0, \"end\": 491.48, \"text\": \"citizen should not be your clickbait. Be better.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 491.48, \"end\": 498.28, \"text\": \"Ivanka Trump tweeted this:\"}, {\"start\": 498.28, \"end\": 503.58, \"text\": \"\\\"She is a young adult and private citizen and should be off-limits.\"}, {\"start\": 506.0, \"end\": 507.86, \"text\": \"A record number of Americans are expected to shop\"}, {\"start\": 507.88, \"end\": 516.12, \"text\": \"online this weekend and on Cyber Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 516.12, \"end\": 525.18, \"text\": \"But experts warn -- online holiday shopping is also prime time for scammers.\"}, {\"start\": 525.18, \"end\": 530.9, \"text\": \"Advice for consumers: Be extra careful shopping on a mobile browser because scammers\"}, {\"start\": 530.9, \"end\": 540.3, \"text\": \"can create fake websites that may look legit.\"}, {\"start\": 540.3, \"end\": 549.26, \"text\": \"Also watch out for fake apps that can steal your personal information or even\"}, {\"start\": 549.26, \"end\": 555.28, \"text\": \"try to extort money by locking your phone.\"}, {\"start\": 555.28, \"end\": 558.98, \"text\": \"You should also avoid clicking on\"}, {\"start\": 558.98, \"end\": 564.22, \"text\": \"any unsolicited emails because that could be phishing.\"}, {\"start\": 564.22, \"end\": 571.94, \"text\": \"And finally make sure to use a website with a valid\"}, {\"start\": 571.94, \"end\": 579.66, \"text\": \"HTTPS connection and a lock signal symbol.\"}, {\"start\": 579.66, \"end\": 589.18, \"text\": \"Experts say websites with just HTTP next to them are more vulnerable to attacks.\"}, {\"start\": 591.3, \"end\": 595.48, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 595.48, \"end\": 597.88, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 597.88, \"end\": 603.62, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 603.62, \"end\": 610.82, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "As0Dy9BpNAk": {
    "video_id": "As0Dy9BpNAk",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.22.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180322",
    "duration": 586,
    "view_count": 1595,
    "description": "3.22.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Dowd resigns as Trump's lawyer\n-Texas bomber leaves behind \"confession\" video\n-Biden: would \"beat the hell\" out of Trump if in high school \n-Airline crew member had cocaine taped to legs\n-House passes \"right to try\" drug bill\n-Repair your credit, beware of scammers\n-Dad recreates fireworks show in daughter's bedroom\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to delive",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.1, \"end\": 9.84, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.84, \"end\": 12.04, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.04, \"end\": 14.06, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 14.06, \"end\": 17.68, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 21.44, \"end\": 25.06, \"text\": \"Shocking news from Washington DC.\"}, {\"start\": 25.06, \"end\": 37.54, \"text\": \"President Trump's lead lawyer in the Russia investigation, John Dowd, resigned today.\"}, {\"start\": 37.62, \"end\": 46.56, \"text\": \"Dowd's resignation comes as Trump has stepped up his attacks on special counsel Robert Mueller\"}, {\"start\": 46.56, \"end\": 54.92, \"text\": \"and right in the midst of negotiations with Mueller's team over a potential interview\"}, {\"start\": 54.92, \"end\": 57.1, \"text\": \"with Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 57.1, \"end\": 64.68, \"text\": \"It's not clear at this point who will take over as lead lawyer for Trump's legal team.\"}, {\"start\": 64.68, \"end\": 71.86, \"text\": \"Dowd's response to CNN: \\\"I love the president and wish him well.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 71.86, \"end\": 78.08, \"text\": \"As we get more information on Dowd's resignation, we will pass it along to you.\"}, {\"start\": 81.22, \"end\": 90.72, \"text\": \"Investigators in Texas say serial bomber Mark Conditt left a 25 minute \\\"confession\\\" video\"}, {\"start\": 90.78, \"end\": 94.36, \"text\": \"on his phone as law enforcement closed in on him.\"}, {\"start\": 94.36, \"end\": 101.84, \"text\": \"Police say the recording gave them a lot of insight into Conditt's troubled state of mind.\"}, {\"start\": 101.84, \"end\": 109.56, \"text\": \"The recording also described in explicit detail the seven homemade bombs Conditt constructed,\"}, {\"start\": 109.64, \"end\": 111.84, \"text\": \"including the one he used to kill himself.\"}, {\"start\": 111.92, \"end\": 123.92, \"text\": \"The only thing the recording did not include was Conditt's motive for terrorizing his own community.\"}, {\"start\": 124.0, \"end\": 133.0, \"text\": \"Police detained and questioned Conditt's two roommates to determine if he was working alone.\"}, {\"start\": 136.4, \"end\": 146.52, \"text\": \"Former Vice President Joe Biden is getting some flak for a speech he made at the University\"}, {\"start\": 146.52, \"end\": 150.6, \"text\": \"of Miami in South Florida on Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 150.6, \"end\": 157.76, \"text\": \"He was talking to the college Democrats about the Access Hollywood video of Trump that surfaced\"}, {\"start\": 157.92, \"end\": 165.0, \"text\": \"in 2016, in which Trump made lewd comments about women.\"}, {\"start\": 165.0, \"end\": 170.28, \"text\": \"Biden said: \\\"A guy who ended up becoming our national leader said I can grab a woman anywhere\"}, {\"start\": 170.28, \"end\": 172.44, \"text\": \"and she likes it.\"}, {\"start\": 172.44, \"end\": 177.6, \"text\": \"And then said, I made a mistake.\"}, {\"start\": 177.6, \"end\": 185.28, \"text\": \"They asked me would I like to debate this gentleman and I said no.\"}, {\"start\": 185.28, \"end\": 195.0, \"text\": \"I said, \\\"If we were in high school I'd take him behind the gym and \\\"beat the hell out of him.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 195.0, \"end\": 197.84, \"text\": \"I've been in a lot of locker rooms my whole life.\"}, {\"start\": 197.84, \"end\": 199.8, \"text\": \"I'm a pretty damn good athlete.\"}, {\"start\": 199.8, \"end\": 208.16, \"text\": \"Any guy that talked that way was usually the fattest, ugliest SOB in the room.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 208.24, \"end\": 214.56, \"text\": \"President Trump immediately flexed his muscles -- on Twitter, of course -- by tweeting:\"}, {\"start\": 214.56, \"end\": 218.16, \"text\": \"\\\"Crazy Joe Biden is trying to act like a tough guy.\"}, {\"start\": 218.16, \"end\": 222.6, \"text\": \"Actually, he is weak, both mentally and physically, and yet he threatens me, for the second time,\"}, {\"start\": 222.6, \"end\": 225.12, \"text\": \"with physical assault.\"}, {\"start\": 225.12, \"end\": 231.72, \"text\": \"He doesn't know me, but he would go down fast and hard, crying all the way.\"}, {\"start\": 231.72, \"end\": 236.64, \"text\": \"Don't threaten people Joe!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 240.32, \"end\": 252.44, \"text\": \"A member of a plane's flight crew got busted for allegedly trying to smuggle 9 pounds of\"}, {\"start\": 252.44, \"end\": 257.19, \"text\": \"cocaine into the United States.\"}, {\"start\": 257.2, \"end\": 262.72, \"text\": \"He landed at New York's JFK airport last Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 262.72, \"end\": 274.36, \"text\": \"The drugs were found during a search, taped around the man's legs.\"}, {\"start\": 274.36, \"end\": 281.52, \"text\": \"US Customs and Border protection identified the man as Hugh Hall, a citizen of Jamaica\"}, {\"start\": 281.52, \"end\": 285.0, \"text\": \"and a crew member for Fly Jamaica Airways.\"}, {\"start\": 285.0, \"end\": 288.56, \"text\": \"The man now faces federal charges.\"}, {\"start\": 291.32, \"end\": 302.96, \"text\": \"The House passed a bill Wednesday that gives terminally ill patients the ability to obtain\"}, {\"start\": 302.96, \"end\": 307.44, \"text\": \"drugs not approved by the FDA.\"}, {\"start\": 307.44, \"end\": 316.74, \"text\": \"The \\\"Right To Try\\\" bill allows dying patients to request drugs from manufacturers that have\"}, {\"start\": 316.74, \"end\": 323.88, \"text\": \"undergone small-scale clinical trials and are currently under FDA consideration.\"}, {\"start\": 323.88, \"end\": 331.72, \"text\": \"Only two Republicans voted against the bill while 35 Democrats crossed the aisle to support it.\"}, {\"start\": 331.72, \"end\": 339.72, \"text\": \"Democratic opponents say it jeopardizes patient safety because the drugs have only been tested\"}, {\"start\": 339.72, \"end\": 344.2, \"text\": \"for safety and not effectiveness or side effects.\"}, {\"start\": 344.2, \"end\": 350.8, \"text\": \"Republican lawmakers and President Trump support the bill, saying the covered drugs are safe\"}, {\"start\": 351.04, \"end\": 357.64, \"text\": \"and terminally ill patients don't have time to wait years for FDA approval.\"}, {\"start\": 357.64, \"end\": 362.36, \"text\": \"The bill now heads to the Senate, where a different version of it passed unanimously\"}, {\"start\": 362.36, \"end\": 366.44, \"text\": \"over the summer.\"}, {\"start\": 370.0, \"end\": 373.04, \"text\": \"What's your credit score?\"}, {\"start\": 373.04, \"end\": 377.68, \"text\": \"If you want to make your score better, be careful.\"}, {\"start\": 377.68, \"end\": 387.56, \"text\": \"Scammers can not only steal your information but may also turn you into a crook.\"}, {\"start\": 387.72, \"end\": 394.2, \"text\": \"According to the Federal Trade Commission there are a few easy ways to spot a credit\"}, {\"start\": 394.2, \"end\": 399.76, \"text\": \"repair scam.\"}, {\"start\": 399.76, \"end\": 408.28, \"text\": \"First -- if the company asked for payment before they render any services.\"}, {\"start\": 408.28, \"end\": 414.88, \"text\": \"Also if they ask that you do not contact the credit reporting agencies directly.\"}, {\"start\": 414.88, \"end\": 424.56, \"text\": \"And if they suggest giving false information when applying for a mortgage or loan.\"}, {\"start\": 424.68, \"end\": 433.44, \"text\": \"Another troubling trend among credit repair scammers is the promise of an entirely new\"}, {\"start\": 433.44, \"end\": 438.64, \"text\": \"credit identity, which can unwittingly land a consumer in trouble with the law.\"}, {\"start\": 438.64, \"end\": 445.55, \"text\": \"You can spot these scams when a service suggests you don't use your Social Security number\"}, {\"start\": 445.56, \"end\": 449.12, \"text\": \"as a primary source of identification.\"}, {\"start\": 449.12, \"end\": 458.08, \"text\": \"Instead they want you to use a new number they assign called a \\\"credit privacy number\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 458.08, \"end\": 462.36, \"text\": \"or \\\"credit profile number\\\" (CPN).\"}, {\"start\": 462.36, \"end\": 468.16, \"text\": \"In many cases these numbers are stolen Social Security numbers, often from children, which\"}, {\"start\": 468.16, \"end\": 472.24, \"text\": \"is why they have a clean credit slate.\"}, {\"start\": 472.24, \"end\": 482.24, \"text\": \"And it can turn an innocent consumer into an unknowing identity thief.\"}, {\"start\": 482.24, \"end\": 485.08, \"text\": \"So be careful.\"}, {\"start\": 488.4, \"end\": 501.639, \"text\": \"Nevada dad Lyle Coram has re-created Disneyland's iconic fireworks show in his daughter Shelby's\"}, {\"start\": 501.64, \"end\": 505.24, \"text\": \"bedroom.\"}, {\"start\": 508.24, \"end\": 514.08, \"text\": \"Coram works as a stagehand on live shows in Las Vegas.\"}, {\"start\": 514.08, \"end\": 519.04, \"text\": \"His technical expertise came in handy on the bedroom project.\"}, {\"start\": 519.04, \"end\": 531.16, \"text\": \"He used a combination of fiber optics, LED lighting and a projector.\"}, {\"start\": 531.2, \"end\": 535.56, \"text\": \"It took about three months to build.\"}, {\"start\": 535.56, \"end\": 543.32, \"text\": \"He even added features like a \\\"Star Wars\\\" theme.\"}, {\"start\": 543.4, \"end\": 551.08, \"text\": \"Coram says his daughter loves Disneyland and the nightly fireworks show is her favorite part.\"}, {\"start\": 551.2, \"end\": 558.8, \"text\": \"Now she can enjoy them every night.\"}, {\"start\": 561.04, \"end\": 564.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 564.0, \"end\": 565.56, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 565.56, \"end\": 567.56, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 567.56, \"end\": 572.16, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 572.16, \"end\": 578.2, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "RrRK1s6vlBU": {
    "video_id": "RrRK1s6vlBU",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.5.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180306",
    "duration": 404,
    "view_count": 1298,
    "description": "3.5.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Police need public's help identifying remains found\n-Trump's DACA deadline passes\n-Congress considers 3-digit national suicide hotline\n-Bill Cosby back in court\n-W. Virginia teacher's strike enters 8th day\n-Trump meets with Israeli Prime Minister\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Lan",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.32, \"end\": 8.38, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.38, \"end\": 10.36, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.36, \"end\": 11.96, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 11.96, \"end\": 15.72, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.36, \"end\": 26.64, \"text\": \"Toronto police are hoping the public can help them identify this man.\"}, {\"start\": 26.64, \"end\": 39.04, \"text\": \"Investigators believe he is a victim connected to a suspected serial killer named Bruce McArthur.\"}, {\"start\": 39.04, \"end\": 49.24, \"text\": \"McArthur was arrested earlier this year and has been charged with six counts of first-degree\"}, {\"start\": 49.24, \"end\": 53.36, \"text\": \"murder in connection with missing persons cases dating back as far as 2010.\"}, {\"start\": 53.36, \"end\": 59.88, \"text\": \"Police say MacArthur buried his victim's body parts in potted plants on properties where\"}, {\"start\": 59.88, \"end\": 62.6, \"text\": \"he worked.\"}, {\"start\": 62.6, \"end\": 67.82, \"text\": \"On Monday police discovered a seventh set of human remains related to the case.\"}, {\"start\": 67.82, \"end\": 71.92, \"text\": \"The body was decomposing inside potted plants.\"}, {\"start\": 71.92, \"end\": 78.3, \"text\": \"They released this photo of the victim's bearded face and is asking for the public's help in\"}, {\"start\": 78.3, \"end\": 80.76, \"text\": \"identifying the man.\"}, {\"start\": 83.26, \"end\": 91.06, \"text\": \"In January President Trump said March 5th would be the day he would end DACA.\"}, {\"start\": 91.06, \"end\": 96.04, \"text\": \"But that deadline is now relatively worthless because court decisions have forced the White\"}, {\"start\": 96.04, \"end\": 104.0, \"text\": \"House to keep renewing DACA permits until further notice.\"}, {\"start\": 104.0, \"end\": 112.62, \"text\": \"However that doesn't mean \\\"dreamers\\\" are sleeping any easier.\"}, {\"start\": 112.62, \"end\": 117.52, \"text\": \"Seven-hundred thousand DACA recipients are now left in limbo, not knowing if they will\"}, {\"start\": 117.52, \"end\": 120.02, \"text\": \"be deported.\"}, {\"start\": 120.02, \"end\": 126.399, \"text\": \"That's why hundreds of DACA recipients and supporters protested at the Capitol in Washington\"}, {\"start\": 126.399, \"end\": 127.959, \"text\": \"DC today.\"}, {\"start\": 127.959, \"end\": 130.32, \"text\": \"They are pushing for immediate action and advocacy.\"}, {\"start\": 130.32, \"end\": 137.2, \"text\": \"But since a Senate attempt to pass legislation on immigration failed, Congress has backed\"}, {\"start\": 137.2, \"end\": 140.72, \"text\": \"off the issue.\"}, {\"start\": 143.76, \"end\": 155.2, \"text\": \"US lawmakers are considering a bill to create a three-digit suicide prevention hotline.\"}, {\"start\": 155.2, \"end\": 163.68, \"text\": \"It would replace the current hotline at 1-800-273-TALK.\"}, {\"start\": 163.68, \"end\": 168.39, \"text\": \"Some people say that number is too hard to remember, especially for those experiencing\"}, {\"start\": 168.4, \"end\": 170.88, \"text\": \"a suicide emergency.\"}, {\"start\": 170.88, \"end\": 179.6, \"text\": \"However studies show when people use the hotline, the risk of suicide sharply drops.\"}, {\"start\": 179.6, \"end\": 190.24, \"text\": \"Sponsors of the bill say a new three-digit hotline has strong bipartisan support.\"}, {\"start\": 190.24, \"end\": 201.2, \"text\": \"Two million people called the crisis line in 2017, up from 1.5 million in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 204.08, \"end\": 216.72, \"text\": \"Bill Cosby is in a Pennsylvania court trying to stop some of his accusers from testifying.\"}, {\"start\": 216.72, \"end\": 221.12, \"text\": \"The two day hearing is part of Cosby's retrial on sex assault charges.\"}, {\"start\": 221.12, \"end\": 227.81, \"text\": \"Cosby's first trial ended in a mistrial last June.\"}, {\"start\": 227.84, \"end\": 233.92, \"text\": \"This time, prosecutors are asking for 19 Cosby accusers to be allowed to testify.\"}, {\"start\": 233.92, \"end\": 240.24, \"text\": \"But Cosby's lawyers say they would need more time to present their case if other accusers\"}, {\"start\": 240.24, \"end\": 243.52, \"text\": \"are given a chance to testify.\"}, {\"start\": 243.54, \"end\": 251.86, \"text\": \"And his lawyers want to present a witness who said Cosby's accuser, Andrea Constand,\"}, {\"start\": 251.86, \"end\": 259.28, \"text\": \"told her she would make a lot of money by making a false sexual assault claim.\"}, {\"start\": 259.28, \"end\": 264.8, \"text\": \"Jury selection is slated to begin March 29th.\"}, {\"start\": 267.84, \"end\": 278.56, \"text\": \"Last week, the teachers union leaders reached a deal with West Virginia governor Jim Justice\"}, {\"start\": 278.56, \"end\": 282.56, \"text\": \"to receive a 5% pay raise.\"}, {\"start\": 282.56, \"end\": 290.24, \"text\": \"The state House approved the raise and the teacher's strike ended.\"}, {\"start\": 290.24, \"end\": 295.92, \"text\": \"But the Senate would only pass a 4% raise.\"}, {\"start\": 295.92, \"end\": 303.68, \"text\": \"So 20,000 teachers and service workers walked out again.\"}, {\"start\": 303.68, \"end\": 308.48, \"text\": \"But this time union leaders say teachers will not return to the class until they get the\"}, {\"start\": 308.48, \"end\": 311.52, \"text\": \"agreed-upon deal.\"}, {\"start\": 311.52, \"end\": 317.28, \"text\": \"Lawmakers are meeting on Monday to work out a solution.\"}, {\"start\": 317.28, \"end\": 325.6, \"text\": \"Until that happens, 277,000 students are out of class.\"}, {\"start\": 330.24, \"end\": 341.84, \"text\": \"Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu made a brief visit to the White House today.\"}, {\"start\": 341.92, \"end\": 348.4, \"text\": \"He is in the US to speak in front of America's biggest pro-Israel group.\"}, {\"start\": 348.4, \"end\": 354.24, \"text\": \"He also took the time to publicly thank President Trump for making the bold, but controversial,\"}, {\"start\": 354.32, \"end\": 361.44, \"text\": \"decision to move the US Embassy from Tel Aviv to Jerusalem.\"}, {\"start\": 361.44, \"end\": 365.12, \"text\": \"Netanyahu's visit is also shrouded in scandal.\"}, {\"start\": 365.12, \"end\": 370.0, \"text\": \"He is at the center of a major corruption scandal in his own country.\"}, {\"start\": 370.0, \"end\": 373.12, \"text\": \"He has denied any wrongdoing.\"}, {\"start\": 376.2, \"end\": 378.78, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 378.78, \"end\": 380.16, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 380.16, \"end\": 382.76, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 382.76, \"end\": 388.18, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 388.18, \"end\": 394.98, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "3mfHu_ianaQ": {
    "video_id": "3mfHu_ianaQ",
    "title": "4.29.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180430",
    "duration": 554,
    "view_count": 2481,
    "description": "4.29.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Migrant caravan reaches U.S. border\n-\"Avengers Infinity War\" shatters records \n-Trump says he had everything to do with N & S Korea meeting\n-Suspected cop killer arrested\n-Allison Mack sex trafficking story explained\n-T-Mobile hiring thousands after merger with Sprint\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from n",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.82, \"end\": 9.52, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.52, \"end\": 11.48, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.48, \"end\": 13.0, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 13.0, \"end\": 16.86, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.18, \"end\": 27.48, \"text\": \"After one month and thousands of grueling miles, hundreds of migrants from Central America\"}, {\"start\": 27.48, \"end\": 31.0, \"text\": \"finally arrived at the US-Mexico border.\"}, {\"start\": 31.0, \"end\": 39.62, \"text\": \"To signify their great sense of accomplishment, there was a big cheer and rally when the caravan\"}, {\"start\": 39.62, \"end\": 41.26, \"text\": \"reached the border.\"}, {\"start\": 41.28, \"end\": 49.38, \"text\": \"Some people climbed the border fence, sat on top and looked around but did not cross\"}, {\"start\": 49.38, \"end\": 52.24, \"text\": \"over into the United States.\"}, {\"start\": 52.24, \"end\": 58.82, \"text\": \"Others shouted \\\"We are not criminals!\"}, {\"start\": 58.82, \"end\": 62.6, \"text\": \"We just want a better life!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 62.6, \"end\": 68.42, \"text\": \"As a caravan reached the US-Mexico border supporters on the San Diego side rallied to\"}, {\"start\": 68.42, \"end\": 70.74, \"text\": \"welcome them.\"}, {\"start\": 70.74, \"end\": 77.26, \"text\": \"Activists from around the country held the \\\"March Without Borders\\\" to show solidarity\"}, {\"start\": 77.26, \"end\": 79.95, \"text\": \"with and support for the caravan.\"}, {\"start\": 79.95, \"end\": 85.979, \"text\": \"The migrants say they will not sneak across the border but plan to turn themselves in\"}, {\"start\": 85.98, \"end\": 88.38, \"text\": \"peacefully and asked for asylum.\"}, {\"start\": 88.38, \"end\": 96.3, \"text\": \"International law requires the US to consider their asylum claims.\"}, {\"start\": 99.74, \"end\": 111.34, \"text\": \"\\\"Avengers: Infinity War\\\" lived up to the hype and set the record books ablaze.\"}, {\"start\": 111.34, \"end\": 120.34, \"text\": \"The movie took in an estimated $880 million worldwide over its opening weekend, $250 million\"}, {\"start\": 120.34, \"end\": 128.26, \"text\": \"in the US and $630 million overseas, both all-time highs.\"}, {\"start\": 128.26, \"end\": 133.66, \"text\": \"That shatters a previous record for biggest US opening weekend ever, edging out 2015 \\\"Star\"}, {\"start\": 133.66, \"end\": 146.18, \"text\": \"Wars: The Force Awakens.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 146.18, \"end\": 151.14, \"text\": \"\\\"Avengers: Infinity War\\\" also blew through the record for biggest global opening, set\"}, {\"start\": 151.14, \"end\": 162.12, \"text\": \"by \\\"Fate of the Furious,\\\" also released in 2015.\"}, {\"start\": 162.12, \"end\": 172.9, \"text\": \"Paramount's \\\"A Quiet Place\\\" came in a distant second at the box office.\"}, {\"start\": 172.9, \"end\": 182.36, \"text\": \"It made an estimated $10.6 million this weekend, putting its total receipts since release just\"}, {\"start\": 182.36, \"end\": 185.15, \"text\": \"of $150 million.\"}, {\"start\": 185.15, \"end\": 195.5, \"text\": \"\\\"I Feel Pretty\\\" landed in third place with an estimated $8.1 million in box office receipts.\"}, {\"start\": 200.7, \"end\": 216.16, \"text\": \"President Trump told a group of supporters in Michigan that he is responsible for Friday's\"}, {\"start\": 216.16, \"end\": 231.56, \"text\": \"historic meeting between North Korean leader Kim Jong-Un and South Korean leader Moon Jae-In.\"}, {\"start\": 231.56, \"end\": 236.74, \"text\": \"During the meeting, both leaders issued a statement calling for an official end to the\"}, {\"start\": 236.74, \"end\": 244.24, \"text\": \"Korean War and issued a commitment to denuclearize the Peninsula.\"}, {\"start\": 244.24, \"end\": 253.1, \"text\": \"Kim says he's planning to close North Korea's nuclear test site next month.\"}, {\"start\": 253.1, \"end\": 264.78, \"text\": \"Kim says North Korea will have no need for nuclear weapons if non-aggression can be promised.\"}, {\"start\": 264.78, \"end\": 272.54, \"text\": \"And now millions across both Koreas and around the world wait to see what will happen when\"}, {\"start\": 272.54, \"end\": 276.44, \"text\": \"President Trump comes to the table.\"}, {\"start\": 276.45, \"end\": 283.61, \"text\": \"The date and time set for a meeting between Trump and Kim will be determined once an agreed-upon\"}, {\"start\": 283.61, \"end\": 285.9, \"text\": \"location is set.\"}, {\"start\": 288.18, \"end\": 299.92, \"text\": \"Last night police in Maine released this picture of suspected cop killer John Williams.\"}, {\"start\": 299.92, \"end\": 306.52, \"text\": \"Police say they pulled back Williams' head by his hair so his face would face the\"}, {\"start\": 306.52, \"end\": 308.62, \"text\": \"camera to confirm his identity.\"}, {\"start\": 308.62, \"end\": 318.5, \"text\": \"Williams is accused of shooting and killing 13-year police veteran Eugene Cole, stealing\"}, {\"start\": 318.5, \"end\": 327.2, \"text\": \"his police cruiser and robbing a store before fleeing on foot.\"}, {\"start\": 327.2, \"end\": 332.96, \"text\": \"Williams was on the run for four days.\"}, {\"start\": 332.96, \"end\": 344.4, \"text\": \"The seven-man capture team say they used Cole's handcuffs to arrest Williams.\"}, {\"start\": 344.4, \"end\": 353.58, \"text\": \"Cole's brother said it made him smile when he heard of the symbolic gesture.\"}, {\"start\": 357.24, \"end\": 365.3, \"text\": \"One of our Sign1News viewers contacted us to get a better explanation of the Allison\"}, {\"start\": 365.3, \"end\": 367.16, \"text\": \"Mack story.\"}, {\"start\": 367.16, \"end\": 370.48, \"text\": \"We are happy to oblige.\"}, {\"start\": 370.48, \"end\": 381.22, \"text\": \"For those of you who may not know, Mack starred in the popular CW television series \\\"Smallville.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 381.22, \"end\": 389.52, \"text\": \"She played the role of Clark Kent's confidant Chloe.\"}, {\"start\": 389.52, \"end\": 402.04, \"text\": \"On Friday she was indicted on charges of sex trafficking, sex trafficking conspiracy and\"}, {\"start\": 402.04, \"end\": 405.08, \"text\": \"forced labor conspiracy.\"}, {\"start\": 405.08, \"end\": 411.48, \"text\": \"She was allegedly involved in an organization call NXIVM.\"}, {\"start\": 411.48, \"end\": 418.86, \"text\": \"Investigators say the group posed as a self-help group but in reality was a scheme in which\"}, {\"start\": 418.86, \"end\": 422.16, \"text\": \"women were exploited sexually.\"}, {\"start\": 422.16, \"end\": 431.9, \"text\": \"Mack is accused of recruiting women into the group to perform sex acts with the group's\"}, {\"start\": 431.9, \"end\": 435.58, \"text\": \"founder Keith Raniere.\"}, {\"start\": 435.58, \"end\": 441.96, \"text\": \"Investigators say until women recruited others, they were called \\\"slaves.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 441.96, \"end\": 446.86, \"text\": \"Those who successfully recruited others were called \\\"masters.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 446.86, \"end\": 452.44, \"text\": \"Mack entered a plea of not guilty.\"}, {\"start\": 452.44, \"end\": 458.76, \"text\": \"Right after her indictment Mack was released on a $5 million bond.\"}, {\"start\": 458.76, \"end\": 463.42, \"text\": \"She's currently under house arrest and can have no contact with NXIVM members or have\"}, {\"start\": 463.42, \"end\": 465.56, \"text\": \"access to the internet or computers.\"}, {\"start\": 465.6, \"end\": 470.14, \"text\": \"She is currently in the process of negotiating a deal with prosecutors.\"}, {\"start\": 472.02, \"end\": 482.92, \"text\": \"After years of negotiating, T-Mobile and Sprint have finally agreed to a massive merger.\"}, {\"start\": 482.92, \"end\": 489.66, \"text\": \"The combined merger will take on the name T-Mobile and would leave just three wireless\"}, {\"start\": 489.66, \"end\": 495.82, \"text\": \"carriers in the US, including Verizon and AT&amp;T.\"}, {\"start\": 495.82, \"end\": 509.14, \"text\": \"T-Mobile CEO John Legrere says he plans to deliver the highest capacity network in US\"}, {\"start\": 509.14, \"end\": 517.14, \"text\": \"history so the company will have to hire thousands of people to install hundreds of thousands\"}, {\"start\": 517.14, \"end\": 519.88, \"text\": \"of antennas across the country to become the leader in 5G connectivity.\"}, {\"start\": 519.88, \"end\": 525.84, \"text\": \"No word yet on when the hiring process will start but as soon as we know we will pass\"}, {\"start\": 525.84, \"end\": 527.94, \"text\": \"along the information to you.\"}, {\"start\": 529.98, \"end\": 532.42, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 532.5, \"end\": 533.98, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 533.98, \"end\": 536.5, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 536.5, \"end\": 540.24, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 540.24, \"end\": 541.54, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 541.54, \"end\": 542.84, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 542.84, \"end\": 546.78, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "wPqsN_awKQ0": {
    "video_id": "wPqsN_awKQ0",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.30.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171031",
    "duration": 461,
    "view_count": 274,
    "description": "October 30, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-MANAFORT AND GATES INDICTED\n-LIST OF CHARGES\n-TRUMP RESPONSE TO INDICTMENTS  \n-KEVIN SPACEY FACES BACKLASH FOR APOLOGY TWEET  \n-10-YEAR OLD BOY LEADS POLICE ON 100 MPH CHASE  \n-MICHAEL JACKSON HIGHEST EARNING DEAD CELEBRITY \n-HALLOWEEN SPENDING TO REACH $9 BILLION\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 11.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 11.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.0, \"end\": 21.0, \"text\": \"This morning two former Trump campaign officials\"}, {\"start\": 22.0, \"end\": 25.0, \"text\": \"turned themselves in to federal authorities.\"}, {\"start\": 27.0, \"end\": 31.0, \"text\": \"Former campaign chairman\"}, {\"start\": 32.0, \"end\": 37.0, \"text\": \"Paul Manafort and former\"}, {\"start\": 37.0, \"end\": 42.0, \"text\": \"campaign deputy Rick Gates\"}, {\"start\": 43.0, \"end\": 48.0, \"text\": \"surrendered at the FBI field office in Washington D.C..\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"These are the first arrests made in special counsel\"}, {\"start\": 54.0, \"end\": 59.0, \"text\": \"Robert Mueller's probe into\"}, {\"start\": 59.0, \"end\": 63.0, \"text\": \"whether Russians meddled in the 2016 presidential election.\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 69.0, \"text\": \"But it's important to note that these initial arrests do not\"}, {\"start\": 69.0, \"end\": 73.0, \"text\": \"cover any activities related to the 2016\"}, {\"start\": 73.0, \"end\": 78.0, \"text\": \"campaign. But it's possible additional charges\"}, {\"start\": 78.0, \"end\": 82.0, \"text\": \"could come later. Also today\"}, {\"start\": 82.0, \"end\": 87.0, \"text\": \"George Papadopoulos,\"}, {\"start\": 87.0, \"end\": 92.0, \"text\": \"a former foreign policy adviser to the Trump campaign,\"}, {\"start\": 93.0, \"end\": 99.0, \"text\": \"pleaded guilty to making false statements to the FBI.\"}, {\"start\": 99.0, \"end\": 104.0, \"text\": \"He admits to lying about his interactions with\"}, {\"start\": 104.0, \"end\": 111.0, \"text\": \"foreign officials close to the Russian government.\"}, {\"start\": 114.0, \"end\": 118.0, \"text\": \"The indictment against Manafort\"}, {\"start\": 119.0, \"end\": 124.0, \"text\": \"and Gates contains 12 counts.\"}, {\"start\": 124.0, \"end\": 127.0, \"text\": \"Here is a list of a few of the charges.\"}, {\"start\": 130.0, \"end\": 134.0, \"text\": \"Investigators say both men received tens of\"}, {\"start\": 134.0, \"end\": 139.0, \"text\": \"millions of dollars for their political consulting\"}, {\"start\": 139.0, \"end\": 144.0, \"text\": \"work with Ukraine.\"}, {\"start\": 144.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"To hide the income, they laundered the money through\"}, {\"start\": 149.0, \"end\": 152.0, \"text\": \"dozens of U.S. and foreign corporations,\"}, {\"start\": 153.0, \"end\": 157.0, \"text\": \"partnerships and bank accounts to make it look like the money\"}, {\"start\": 157.0, \"end\": 162.0, \"text\": \"came from a legitimate company and not from illegal dealings with Ukraine.\"}, {\"start\": 164.001, \"end\": 166.999, \"text\": \"President Trump has not said much since the\"}, {\"start\": 167.0, \"end\": 172.0, \"text\": \"indictments were handed down. His only response so far is\"}, {\"start\": 172.0, \"end\": 176.0, \"text\": \"this tweet which says \\\"Sorry but this is years ago before\"}, {\"start\": 176.0, \"end\": 181.0, \"text\": \"Paul Manafort was part of the campaign. But why\"}, {\"start\": 181.0, \"end\": 186.0, \"text\": \"aren't crooked Hillary and the Dems the focus?\"}, {\"start\": 186.0, \"end\": 191.0, \"text\": \"Also there is no collusion!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 193.0, \"end\": 197.0, \"text\": \"Actor Anthony Rapp has come forward\"}, {\"start\": 197.0, \"end\": 202.0, \"text\": \"and accused actor Kevin Spacey of\"}, {\"start\": 202.0, \"end\": 207.0, \"text\": \"making sexual advances. Rapp says the incident occurred 30 years ago\"}, {\"start\": 207.0, \"end\": 213.0, \"text\": \"when he was 14 years old and Spacey was 26.\"}, {\"start\": 213.0, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"Both men were working on Broadway at the time\"}, {\"start\": 218.0, \"end\": 224.0, \"text\": \"and Rapp went to a party at Spacey's apartment.\"}, {\"start\": 224.0, \"end\": 229.0, \"text\": \"Spacey issued a statement saying he didn't\"}, {\"start\": 229.0, \"end\": 233.0, \"text\": \"remember the incident but he offered an\"}, {\"start\": 233.0, \"end\": 238.0, \"text\": \"apology to Rapp saying he could have been\"}, {\"start\": 238.0, \"end\": 244.0, \"text\": \"drunk at the time and acted inappropriately.\"}, {\"start\": 245.0, \"end\": 249.0, \"text\": \"Spacey also used the opportunity to come out\"}, {\"start\": 249.0, \"end\": 251.0, \"text\": \"of the closet as a gay man.\"}, {\"start\": 251.0, \"end\": 257.0, \"text\": \"Many Hollywood celebrities quickly criticized Spacey for his so-called apology.\"}, {\"start\": 259.0, \"end\": 263.0, \"text\": \"Many critics are saying Spacey admitted to being gay to\"}, {\"start\": 263.0, \"end\": 268.0, \"text\": \"draw attention away from the fact that\"}, {\"start\": 268.0, \"end\": 276.0, \"text\": \"he's accused of sexually harassing a child.\"}, {\"start\": 278.0, \"end\": 281.0, \"text\": \"Take a look at this video. It shows a\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 289.0, \"text\": \"10 year old boy leading Ohio State Highway Patrol\"}, {\"start\": 289.024, \"end\": 291.024, \"text\": \"on an hour long car chase.\"}, {\"start\": 291.1, \"end\": 296.1, \"text\": \"Authorities were called after the boy allegedly stole his mother's\"}, {\"start\": 297.0, \"end\": 302.0, \"text\": \"boyfriend's car. Police say the stolen vehicle topped nearly 100 miles\"}, {\"start\": 302.0, \"end\": 307.0, \"text\": \"per hour at one point. Troopers deployed stop sticks\"}, {\"start\": 308.0, \"end\": 313.0, \"text\": \"forcing the boy to veer off the road.\"}, {\"start\": 313.0, \"end\": 319.0, \"text\": \"They caught up to the boy, boxed him in and ended the chase.\"}, {\"start\": 320.0, \"end\": 323.0, \"text\": \"No one was injured. The boy was safely\"}, {\"start\": 324.0, \"end\": 329.0, \"text\": \"taken into custody. Police say it was a second time\"}, {\"start\": 329.0, \"end\": 333.0, \"text\": \"in two weeks the boy had stolen a car and taken it for a joy ride.\"}, {\"start\": 335.0, \"end\": 339.0, \"text\": \"For the fifth year in a row Michael Jackson is the\"}, {\"start\": 339.0, \"end\": 347.0, \"text\": \"highest paid dead celebrity.\"}, {\"start\": 347.0, \"end\": 352.0, \"text\": \"Hiis estate pulled in seventy five million dollars this year.\"}, {\"start\": 352.0, \"end\": 357.0, \"text\": \"Ventures like the Cirque du Soleil show in\"}, {\"start\": 357.0, \"end\": 361.0, \"text\": \"Las Vegas and a\"}, {\"start\": 361.0, \"end\": 366.0, \"text\": \"percentage of the EMI Music publishing catalog\"}, {\"start\": 366.0, \"end\": 368.0, \"text\": \"produce a steady stream of income.\"}, {\"start\": 369.001, \"end\": 370.999, \"text\": \"This year two new money-making\"}, {\"start\": 371.0, \"end\": 376.0, \"text\": \"ventures were added -- a TV Halloween special and\"}, {\"start\": 376.0, \"end\": 380.0, \"text\": \"the \\\"Scream\\\" album which is a\"}, {\"start\": 380.0, \"end\": 384.0, \"text\": \"compilation of Halloween themed songs.\"}, {\"start\": 389.0, \"end\": 394.0, \"text\": \"According to a survey by the National\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"Retail Federation,\"}, {\"start\": 399.0, \"end\": 403.0, \"text\": \"retailers are set to rake in 9.1 billion dollars\"}, {\"start\": 403.0, \"end\": 408.0, \"text\": \"in Halloween sales this year. Shoppers are expected to spend 3.4 billion dollars\"}, {\"start\": 408.0, \"end\": 412.0, \"text\": \"on costumes,\"}, {\"start\": 413.0, \"end\": 417.0, \"text\": \"2.7 billion on candy and 2.7 billion\"}, {\"start\": 417.0, \"end\": 421.0, \"text\": \"on decorations.\"}, {\"start\": 421.0, \"end\": 424.0, \"text\": \"If the survey data is\"}, {\"start\": 425.0, \"end\": 429.0, \"text\": \"correct, 2017 sales will be an\"}, {\"start\": 429.0, \"end\": 435.0, \"text\": \"8.3 percent jump from last year's sales.\"}, {\"start\": 438.024, \"end\": 441.099, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories. I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 441.1, \"end\": 443.1, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 443.1, \"end\": 447.1, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 447.124, \"end\": 449.124, \"text\": \"Sign1News. You life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "hpgrcRBoz4M": {
    "video_id": "hpgrcRBoz4M",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.26.18",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20181227",
    "duration": 594,
    "view_count": 1273,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-CBP announces changes after another child dies in custody\n-Gun deaths in U.S. reach record high\n-Mom gifted bear with dead son’s voice recording\n-‘Empire’ star proposes to ex-wife\n-1st trailer released for Jordan Peele’s new movie “Us”\n-Deaf instructors prepare future interpreters",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 23.98, \"end\": 25.04, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 25.04, \"end\": 27.3, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 27.3, \"end\": 28.94, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 28.94, \"end\": 31.78, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 38.86, \"end\": 48.86, \"text\": \"U.S. Customs and Border Protection (CBP) has announced policy changes after a second Guatemalan\"}, {\"start\": 48.86, \"end\": 52.86, \"text\": \"child's death in US custody.\"}, {\"start\": 52.86, \"end\": 67.44, \"text\": \"The boy was identified as eight-year-old Felipe Alonzo Gomez by US representative Joaquin Castro.\"}, {\"start\": 67.44, \"end\": 74.2, \"text\": \"Felipe and his father were detained by customs agents on December 18.\"}, {\"start\": 74.2, \"end\": 79.94, \"text\": \"Felipe became ill and died on Monday, Christmas Eve.\"}, {\"start\": 80.04, \"end\": 83.0, \"text\": \"No cause of death has been released.\"}, {\"start\": 83.0, \"end\": 92.6, \"text\": \"By Tuesday CBP had announced new policy changes, including conducting additional medical checks\"}, {\"start\": 92.6, \"end\": 99.32, \"text\": \"on children in CBP custody and reviewing other custody options to help relieve overcrowding\"}, {\"start\": 99.32, \"end\": 102.6, \"text\": \"issues at CBP's facilities.\"}, {\"start\": 104.76, \"end\": 113.48, \"text\": \"According to a new CDC study, gun violence is on the rise in the US.\"}, {\"start\": 113.48, \"end\": 121.2, \"text\": \"So much so, the CDC calls it a public health epidemic.\"}, {\"start\": 121.2, \"end\": 126.76, \"text\": \"Gun deaths in the United States reached a record high in 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 126.76, \"end\": 133.92, \"text\": \"Almost 40,000 people were killed by firearms last year.\"}, {\"start\": 133.92, \"end\": 137.84, \"text\": \"That's the highest number since 1979.\"}, {\"start\": 137.84, \"end\": 153.72, \"text\": \"The data includes homicide, unintentional deaths, death in war or legal interventions\"}, {\"start\": 153.72, \"end\": 156.6, \"text\": \"and undetermined deaths.\"}, {\"start\": 156.6, \"end\": 165.68, \"text\": \"CNN found that nearly 24,000 of the gun deaths were suicides, the highest rate in 18 years.\"}, {\"start\": 165.68, \"end\": 174.72, \"text\": \"The National Rifle Association says the solution is not in creating more gun laws.\"}, {\"start\": 174.72, \"end\": 185.0, \"text\": \"But gun legislation advocates call the rising numbers proof that the country is facing a\"}, {\"start\": 185.0, \"end\": 187.52, \"text\": \"public health epidemic when it comes to gun violence.\"}, {\"start\": 191.0, \"end\": 198.36, \"text\": \"A touching and poignant Christmas video is generating a lot of interest on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 198.36, \"end\": 210.6, \"text\": \"A mother's police officer son named Sean Tanner died this past October and received a teddy\"}, {\"start\": 210.6, \"end\": 214.8, \"text\": \"bear wearing a police uniform.\"}, {\"start\": 214.8, \"end\": 219.84, \"text\": \"The build-a-bear also plays a recording of officer Tanner's voice, a sound that brought\"}, {\"start\": 219.84, \"end\": 223.4, \"text\": \"tears to his mother's eyes.\"}, {\"start\": 223.4, \"end\": 231.48, \"text\": \"Tanner worked as an officer for the China Lake Police Department in California.\"}, {\"start\": 231.48, \"end\": 237.92, \"text\": \"His sister Brittany came up with the idea of the teddy bear as a gift for their mother.\"}, {\"start\": 242.48, \"end\": 250.96, \"text\": \"Actor Terrence Howard is hoping the second time will be the charm.\"}, {\"start\": 250.96, \"end\": 263.32, \"text\": \"He proposed to his ex-wife Mira Pak three years after they divorced.\"}, {\"start\": 263.32, \"end\": 272.88, \"text\": \"Howard posted an emotional video on Instagram Tuesday to share the news of their engagement\"}, {\"start\": 272.88, \"end\": 277.48, \"text\": \"and some words about finding true love.\"}, {\"start\": 277.48, \"end\": 286.48, \"text\": \"He used the caption \\\"Blood is thicker than water but love is the glue that binds us.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 291.0, \"end\": 300.32, \"text\": \"Jordan Peele has a new movie that he hopes will scare us.\"}, {\"start\": 300.32, \"end\": 309.32, \"text\": \"Peele wrote and directed the Oscar-winning movie \\\"Get Out.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 309.32, \"end\": 317.6, \"text\": \"Today he released the first trailer for his new horror movie \\\"Us.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 318.0, \"end\": 337.0, \"text\": \"It stars Academy Award winning actress Lupita Nyong'o and Winston Duke of \\\"Black Panther.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 337.0, \"end\": 342.24, \"text\": \"The movie is about a family that heads to a beachside house in California for a summer\"}, {\"start\": 342.24, \"end\": 343.92, \"text\": \"getaway.\"}, {\"start\": 343.92, \"end\": 354.84, \"text\": \"When mysterious people show up in their driveway, the family realizes they have evil doppelgangers\"}, {\"start\": 354.84, \"end\": 358.0, \"text\": \"haunting them.\"}, {\"start\": 358.0, \"end\": 369.0, \"text\": \"Doppelganger is a German word that means double of a living person or evil twin.\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 372.52, \"text\": \"\\\"Us\\\" is slated to hit theaters in March.\"}, {\"start\": 378.16, \"end\": 383.92, \"text\": \"Many colleges and universities across the country have sign language interpreter programs\"}, {\"start\": 383.92, \"end\": 389.24, \"text\": \"that train and prepare students to become certified interpreters.\"}, {\"start\": 389.24, \"end\": 392.92, \"text\": \"Many of them are taught by hearing instructors.\"}, {\"start\": 392.92, \"end\": 401.2, \"text\": \"But at Georgia State University, the students learn from the best deaf instructors who provide\"}, {\"start\": 401.2, \"end\": 408.0, \"text\": \"full immersion in Deaf history, Deaf culture and skills development.\"}, {\"start\": 408.0, \"end\": 416.56, \"text\": \"Recently Sign1News anchor Candace Jones was brought in as a guest speaker to expose the\"}, {\"start\": 416.56, \"end\": 420.12, \"text\": \"students to sign language diversity.\"}, {\"start\": 420.12, \"end\": 422.48, \"text\": \"These are the faces\"}, {\"start\": 422.48, \"end\": 428.12, \"text\": \"a future interpreters, soaking in as much knowledge as they can from guest speaker Sign1News\"}, {\"start\": 428.12, \"end\": 434.16, \"text\": \"anchor Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 434.16, \"end\": 440.8, \"text\": \"Class instructor Amy Cohen Efron says her students are not just learning how to sign.\"}, {\"start\": 440.8, \"end\": 450.4, \"text\": \"There also learning to appreciate and respect Deaf history, culture and the depth of the\"}, {\"start\": 450.4, \"end\": 456.52, \"text\": \"Deaf community.\"}, {\"start\": 456.52, \"end\": 464.64, \"text\": \"And being taught by a deaf instructor has a huge impact.\"}, {\"start\": 470.72, \"end\": 474.32, \"text\": \"Many students see me and they become compassionate and passionate about history because they\"}, {\"start\": 474.32, \"end\": 477.32, \"text\": \"can see it through my blood.\"}, {\"start\": 477.32, \"end\": 480.36, \"text\": \"They can see what I experienced growing up.\"}, {\"start\": 486.52, \"end\": 490.04, \"text\": \"Before this interpreter program all of my teachers were hearing.\"}, {\"start\": 490.04, \"end\": 503.4, \"text\": \"I realized my signing, comprehension and receptive skills were good but my skills weren't fully\"}, {\"start\": 503.56, \"end\": 506.36, \"text\": \"developed yet and I wasn't experiencing true immersion.\"}, {\"start\": 506.36, \"end\": 514.64, \"text\": \"But now with a deaf teacher, the experience is so much better and my skills are much smoother.\"}, {\"start\": 514.64, \"end\": 521.76, \"text\": \"Jones is sharing with the students a different Deaf experience and a different language.\"}, {\"start\": 521.76, \"end\": 527.88, \"text\": \"She is teaching students about BASL, Black American sign language.\"}, {\"start\": 533.76, \"end\": 535.76, \"text\": \"I think it's important to expose the students to a variety of sign language styles because\"}, {\"start\": 535.76, \"end\": 537.44, \"text\": \"they are going to meet a variety of clients and people who may use BASL.\"}, {\"start\": 537.44, \"end\": 543.36, \"text\": \"BASL is very new and finally being recognized as its own language.\"}, {\"start\": 543.36, \"end\": 549.52, \"text\": \"For Natasha Patterson, whose parents are deaf, Jones' presentation will ultimately help her\"}, {\"start\": 549.52, \"end\": 554.68, \"text\": \"grow professionally and personally.\"}, {\"start\": 554.68, \"end\": 564.2, \"text\": \"I want to be involved with the Deaf community and also understand who I am and understand\"}, {\"start\": 564.2, \"end\": 565.8, \"text\": \"my parents more.\"}, {\"start\": 566.88, \"end\": 568.92, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 568.92, \"end\": 570.72, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 570.72, \"end\": 573.28, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 573.28, \"end\": 578.2, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 578.2, \"end\": 580.48, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 580.48, \"end\": 582.4, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 582.4, \"end\": 585.44, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "FZ10xSnJCEI": {
    "video_id": "FZ10xSnJCEI",
    "title": "Update: Deadly Miami bridge collapse (ASL - 3.16.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180316",
    "duration": 75,
    "view_count": 87,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.0, \"end\": 8.6, \"text\": \"The Miami pedestrian bridge rescue operation is now a recovery operation.\"}, {\"start\": 8.6, \"end\": 15.78, \"text\": \"Of the six people killed, five bodies are still under the bridge wreckage.\"}, {\"start\": 15.78, \"end\": 24.06, \"text\": \"Officials say their priority now is getting to those remains so they can be taken to a\"}, {\"start\": 24.1, \"end\": 26.78, \"text\": \"proper place of rest.\"}, {\"start\": 26.78, \"end\": 32.22, \"text\": \"The National Transportation Safety Board is on the scene and in the very early stages\"}, {\"start\": 32.22, \"end\": 34.92, \"text\": \"of its investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 34.92, \"end\": 40.5, \"text\": \"Its number one goal is to find out what caused the bridge to collapse so that it doesn't\"}, {\"start\": 40.5, \"end\": 49.52, \"text\": \"happen again and to find out who's responsible.\"}, {\"start\": 49.52, \"end\": 56.16, \"text\": \"The walkway had only been in place a couple of days and was supposed to be completed over\"}, {\"start\": 56.16, \"end\": 58.98, \"text\": \"the next few months.\"}, {\"start\": 58.98, \"end\": 71.16, \"text\": \"Florida Governor Rick Scott said \\\"If anybody has done anything wrong, we will hold them\"}, {\"start\": 71.16, \"end\": 73.9, \"text\": \"accountable.\\\"\"}]"
  },
  "_Q4ShGf3FzY": {
    "video_id": "_Q4ShGf3FzY",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.26.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180427",
    "duration": 320,
    "view_count": 1110,
    "description": "4.26.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Bill Cosby found guilty\n-VA Secretary nominee withdraws\n-Teachers in Arizona walkout over funding and pay raises\n-Trump praises Kamye West after Kayne praises him\n-Happy birthday to First Lady Melania Trump\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN, FOX, A",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.24, \"end\": 9.48, \"text\": \"Hello everyone!\"}, {\"start\": 9.48, \"end\": 12.06, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.06, \"end\": 14.16, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 14.16, \"end\": 18.44, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for the day.\"}, {\"start\": 20.76, \"end\": 31.5, \"text\": \"Bill Cosby is found guilty of three counts of aggravated indecent assault.\"}, {\"start\": 31.5, \"end\": 40.4, \"text\": \"He was on trial for drugging and sexually assaulting a woman at his home in 2004.\"}, {\"start\": 40.4, \"end\": 46.86, \"text\": \"Cosby is 80 years old and he could spend up to 30 years in prison.\"}, {\"start\": 46.86, \"end\": 51.04, \"text\": \"This is the second criminal trial for Cosby.\"}, {\"start\": 51.04, \"end\": 60.92, \"text\": \"The first ended in a hung jury last year.\"}, {\"start\": 60.92, \"end\": 67.3, \"text\": \"Cosby is out on a million dollar bail.\"}, {\"start\": 67.3, \"end\": 78.6, \"text\": \"He is under house arrest until sentencing.\"}, {\"start\": 83.04, \"end\": 92.72, \"text\": \"Rear Admiral Ronny Jackson has withdrawn his nomination as the president's choice to\"}, {\"start\": 92.72, \"end\": 103.0, \"text\": \"lead the Department of Veterans Affairs.\"}, {\"start\": 103.0, \"end\": 112.08, \"text\": \"Jackson's nomination was postponed due to allegations about his professional conduct.\"}, {\"start\": 112.08, \"end\": 125.24, \"text\": \"Jackson issued a statement saying the allegations against him are completely false and fabricated.\"}, {\"start\": 125.24, \"end\": 132.24, \"text\": \"And the allegations have become a distraction for the president.\"}, {\"start\": 136.6, \"end\": 144.56, \"text\": \"More than 100 school districts in Arizona are cancelling classes because of the teacher walkout.\"}, {\"start\": 144.56, \"end\": 151.8, \"text\": \"Teachers are walking out because they want raises and better school funding.\"}, {\"start\": 151.8, \"end\": 160.72, \"text\": \"Arizona is not the only state where teachers are walking out.\"}, {\"start\": 160.72, \"end\": 171.08, \"text\": \"The walkout started in West Virginia and then moved to Oklahoma and Kentucky.\"}, {\"start\": 171.08, \"end\": 177.92, \"text\": \"Arizona's governor says he's pushing for a raise for teachers.\"}, {\"start\": 177.92, \"end\": 181.4, \"text\": \"The schools in Arizona are closed for two days.\"}, {\"start\": 184.72, \"end\": 196.24, \"text\": \"Rapper Kanye West tweeted praises for President\"}, {\"start\": 196.24, \"end\": 209.16, \"text\": \"Trump and social media hasn't stopped talking about it.\"}, {\"start\": 209.16, \"end\": 218.48, \"text\": \"Some people on social media believe West is having mental issues.\"}, {\"start\": 218.48, \"end\": 227.48, \"text\": \"Others say he's creating publicity for soon- to-be-released music.\"}, {\"start\": 227.48, \"end\": 236.24, \"text\": \"His wife, Kim Kardashian West, tweeted the media is trying to label and demonize her\"}, {\"start\": 236.24, \"end\": 243.6, \"text\": \"husband by calling him erratic or disturbing and it is, quote, \\\"scary.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 246.04, \"end\": 251.4, \"text\": \"Today is First Lady Melania Trump's 48th birthday.\"}, {\"start\": 251.4, \"end\": 263.6, \"text\": \"During a phone interview with Fox News,  the president wished Melania happy birthday.\"}, {\"start\": 263.6, \"end\": 270.16, \"text\": \"However, he says he's been too busy to get her a gift.\"}, {\"start\": 270.16, \"end\": 277.56, \"text\": \"In addition to celebrating her birthday, the First Lady and the President are hosting the\"}, {\"start\": 277.56, \"end\": 283.88, \"text\": \"Wounded Warrior Project at the White House.\"}, {\"start\": 288.84, \"end\": 292.08, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for the day.\"}, {\"start\": 292.1, \"end\": 294.09, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 294.09, \"end\": 297.32, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 297.32, \"end\": 302.56, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 302.56, \"end\": 305.32, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 305.32, \"end\": 307.32, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 307.32, \"end\": 312.08, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "1SVT3uqXEAE": {
    "video_id": "1SVT3uqXEAE",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.7.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180208",
    "duration": 614,
    "view_count": 1500,
    "description": "2.7.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-White House aide resigns, denies abusing ex-wives \n-Police plead for help to catch serial shooter \n-Tiger cub found in express mail container \n-Weight Watchers offers teens free membership\n-First music video from \"Black Panther\" album \n-Sign1News fans video of the day\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and informati",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.2, \"end\": 10.18, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 10.18, \"end\": 12.48, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.52, \"end\": 13.72, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.72, \"end\": 16.64, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.98, \"end\": 32.2, \"text\": \"White House staff secretary Rob Porter has resigned amid abuse claims by his two former wives.\"}, {\"start\": 32.2, \"end\": 39.1, \"text\": \"Porter's first wife says he was verbally, emotionally and physically abusive during\"}, {\"start\": 39.1, \"end\": 40.4, \"text\": \"their marriage.\"}, {\"start\": 40.4, \"end\": 47.36, \"text\": \"His second wife reportedly had to receive a temporary emergency protective order in\"}, {\"start\": 47.38, \"end\": 60.28, \"text\": \"2010 when Porter refused to leave her home, a violation of the couple's separation agreement.\"}, {\"start\": 60.32, \"end\": 72.24, \"text\": \"The White House says Porter released a statement denying the claims, calling them outrageous\"}, {\"start\": 72.24, \"end\": 74.22, \"text\": \"and vile.\"}, {\"start\": 74.22, \"end\": 82.2, \"text\": \"Porter resigned even though many White House officials urged him to stay.\"}, {\"start\": 82.2, \"end\": 89.54, \"text\": \"White House Press Secretary Sarah Sanders says Porter's last day on the job has not\"}, {\"start\": 89.56, \"end\": 91.46, \"text\": \"been set.\"}, {\"start\": 91.46, \"end\": 97.28, \"text\": \"He will remain in his position to facilitate a smooth transition to his successor.\"}, {\"start\": 100.3, \"end\": 113.26, \"text\": \"Nevada authorities are pleading for the public's help to catch a serial shooter.\"}, {\"start\": 113.4, \"end\": 127.76, \"text\": \"They say he has shot four homeless men in the Las Vegas area within a week.\"}, {\"start\": 127.76, \"end\": 129.9, \"text\": \"Two of the victims died.\"}, {\"start\": 129.9, \"end\": 132.52, \"text\": \"Three of the men were shot on the same day, January 29th.\"}, {\"start\": 132.52, \"end\": 140.64, \"text\": \"The fourth man was shot four days later on February 2nd while sleeping under a bridge.\"}, {\"start\": 140.64, \"end\": 148.62, \"text\": \"Police say surveillance video captured the suspect killing the fourth man.\"}, {\"start\": 148.62, \"end\": 161.28, \"text\": \"The suspect is described as a white or Hispanic male about 6 feet tall and the vehicle he\"}, {\"start\": 161.28, \"end\": 164.96, \"text\": \"was believed to have been driving is a silver or gray SUV.\"}, {\"start\": 164.96, \"end\": 168.3, \"text\": \"Take a close look at this surveillance video.\"}, {\"start\": 205.98, \"end\": 212.98, \"text\": \"Police are asking anyone with information to contact Crimestoppers.\"}, {\"start\": 215.92, \"end\": 224.46, \"text\": \"Mexican authorities say they rescued a two-month-old Bengal tiger cub from a package intended for\"}, {\"start\": 224.46, \"end\": 230.66, \"text\": \"shipping.\"}, {\"start\": 230.66, \"end\": 239.28, \"text\": \"Officials reportedly heard noises and called in sniffing dogs, who confirmed something\"}, {\"start\": 239.28, \"end\": 243.04, \"text\": \"was alive inside the box.\"}, {\"start\": 243.04, \"end\": 254.3, \"text\": \"Authorities say the cub was completely sedated and had no food or water.\"}, {\"start\": 254.3, \"end\": 264.18, \"text\": \"Bengal tigers are considered endangered.\"}, {\"start\": 264.18, \"end\": 274.2, \"text\": \"The cub is now in the custody of Mexico's Department of Natural Resources and Environment.\"}, {\"start\": 277.38, \"end\": 289.12, \"text\": \"Weight Watchers just announced one of its goals this year: to help 10 million people\"}, {\"start\": 289.12, \"end\": 292.1, \"text\": \"adopt healthy habits.\"}, {\"start\": 292.1, \"end\": 307.94, \"text\": \"Part of that plan is to offer free memberships over the summer to teenagers 13 to 17 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 307.94, \"end\": 315.42, \"text\": \"The company also says it plans to remove all artificial ingredients from products that\"}, {\"start\": 315.42, \"end\": 317.34, \"text\": \"carry the Weight Watchers brand.\"}, {\"start\": 317.34, \"end\": 328.7, \"text\": \"Co-owner Oprah Winfrey released a statement that said: \\\"I am inspired to be part of this\"}, {\"start\": 328.7, \"end\": 334.26, \"text\": \"purpose driven mission as we deepen and expand our own connection to communities, making\"}, {\"start\": 334.26, \"end\": 338.24, \"text\": \"wellness accessible to everyone.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 341.82, \"end\": 365.06, \"text\": \"Grammy award-winning rapper Kendrick Lamar and R&amp;B singer Sza have just debuted the first\"}, {\"start\": 365.06, \"end\": 371.8, \"text\": \"music video from Lamar's \\\"Black Panther: The Album.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 371.8, \"end\": 378.66, \"text\": \"The song is called \\\"All The Stars.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 378.66, \"end\": 385.32, \"text\": \"The music video was directed by Dave Meyers.\"}, {\"start\": 385.32, \"end\": 392.8, \"text\": \"All the songs on the album were inspired by the Black Panther movie.\"}, {\"start\": 392.8, \"end\": 396.8, \"text\": \"The album drops February 9th.\"}, {\"start\": 396.8, \"end\": 403.02, \"text\": \"The movie hits theaters a week later.\"}, {\"start\": 406.4, \"end\": 422.78, \"text\": \"Sign1News fan Nikole Kolenda sent us an adorable video of her son Damon practicing ASL with her.\"}, {\"start\": 422.78, \"end\": 431.32, \"text\": \"Damon is hearing but his father Dillon is a CODA.\"}, {\"start\": 431.32, \"end\": 438.94, \"text\": \"Dillon's parents and several other members of the family are deaf so Damon is learning\"}, {\"start\": 438.94, \"end\": 442.48, \"text\": \"ASL so he can communicate with the extended family.\"}, {\"start\": 442.48, \"end\": 450.74, \"text\": \"Nikole says Damon's signs are not perfect but he sure is expressive!\"}, {\"start\": 450.74, \"end\": 452.2, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 452.28, \"end\": 454.28, \"text\": \"Apple.\"}, {\"start\": 454.76, \"end\": 455.9, \"text\": \"Hurt.\"}, {\"start\": 460.06, \"end\": 462.06, \"text\": \"Airplane. (Nikole: Airplane?) Airplane.\"}, {\"start\": 468.6, \"end\": 470.6, \"text\": \"(Nikole:What's food?) Food.\"}, {\"start\": 471.72, \"end\": 473.72, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's drink?) Eat.\"}, {\"start\": 475.12, \"end\": 477.82, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's drink?) Drink.\"}, {\"start\": 478.96, \"end\": 480.96, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's hot?) Hot. Hot.\"}, {\"start\": 482.28, \"end\": 484.28, \"text\": \"Horsey. (Nikole: Horsey. Yeah.)\"}, {\"start\": 485.18, \"end\": 487.18, \"text\": \"Mamma may I have a drink of water?\"}, {\"start\": 487.18, \"end\": 490.62, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's water?) Water. Water.\"}, {\"start\": 490.62, \"end\": 497.68, \"text\": \"(Nikole: Water. (laughter)) What is the sign for cold?)\"}, {\"start\": 497.82, \"end\": 499.2, \"text\": \"Cold!\"}, {\"start\": 499.92, \"end\": 504.58, \"text\": \"(Nikole: Forgot. (laughter))\"}, {\"start\": 504.58, \"end\": 505.78, \"text\": \"Daddy.\"}, {\"start\": 505.78, \"end\": 508.86, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's mommy?) Mommy.\"}, {\"start\": 508.86, \"end\": 509.46, \"text\": \"(Nikole: Good job.)\"}, {\"start\": 509.46, \"end\": 511.46, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's thank you?) Thank you.\"}, {\"start\": 511.46, \"end\": 515.62, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What is please?) Please.\"}, {\"start\": 517.28, \"end\": 520.74, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What is peach?) Peach.\"}, {\"start\": 520.74, \"end\": 523.76, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's flower?) Flower.\"}, {\"start\": 523.76, \"end\": 524.76, \"text\": \"(Nikole: (laughter) Good job.)\"}, {\"start\": 524.76, \"end\": 529.3, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What is more?) More. More.\"}, {\"start\": 531.22, \"end\": 534.28, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's deer?) Deer.\"}, {\"start\": 536.4, \"end\": 538.4, \"text\": \"(Nikole: What's mad? I'm mad!)\"}, {\"start\": 538.4, \"end\": 541.08, \"text\": \"Yeah!!! (laughter)\"}, {\"start\": 541.08, \"end\": 545.4, \"text\": \"Mad! Mad! Mad!\"}, {\"start\": 546.06, \"end\": 554.48, \"text\": \"Nikole thank you for sending us this adorable video and for encouraging Damon to learn ASL.\"}, {\"start\": 554.64, \"end\": 559.9, \"text\": \"I was born hearing and became deaf at three years old.\"}, {\"start\": 559.9, \"end\": 561.88, \"text\": \"I learned ASL in school.\"}, {\"start\": 561.88, \"end\": 565.32, \"text\": \"My teachers would give me papers with pictures that demonstrated how to sign words.\"}, {\"start\": 565.32, \"end\": 571.04, \"text\": \"I would take those vocabulary words home to show my family so we could learn ASL at the\"}, {\"start\": 571.14, \"end\": 572.66, \"text\": \"same time.\"}, {\"start\": 572.66, \"end\": 578.8, \"text\": \"It is important that children are bilingual, learning both English and ASL.\"}, {\"start\": 578.8, \"end\": 582.8, \"text\": \"Nikole great job!  Keep up the good work.\"}, {\"start\": 585.68, \"end\": 588.8, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 588.8, \"end\": 590.16, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 590.16, \"end\": 593.68, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 593.68, \"end\": 598.96, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 599.2, \"end\": 605.84, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-bM2DBJE7zE": {
    "video_id": "-bM2DBJE7zE",
    "title": "Get some rest! “It’s World Sleep Day” (ASL - 3.16.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180316",
    "duration": 77,
    "view_count": 474,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.54, \"end\": 7.42, \"text\": \"If your boss catches you napping on the job or your teacher scolds you for falling asleep\"}, {\"start\": 7.42, \"end\": 13.16, \"text\": \"in class, just tell them you have a really good excuse.\"}, {\"start\": 13.16, \"end\": 17.02, \"text\": \"Today is \\\"World Sleep Day!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 17.02, \"end\": 25.16, \"text\": \"World Sleep Day was started in 2008 by the World Sleep Society and is designed to draw\"}, {\"start\": 25.16, \"end\": 30.92, \"text\": \"attention to the importance of and benefits associated with good, healthy sleep.\"}, {\"start\": 30.92, \"end\": 38.32, \"text\": \"According to several studies, sleep deprivation is a global epidemic that can lead to weight\"}, {\"start\": 38.32, \"end\": 55.64, \"text\": \"gain, mood swings, memory loss, depression and increase your risk of heart disease and stroke.\"}, {\"start\": 55.64, \"end\": 61.64, \"text\": \"It is also estimated sleep deprivation costs the US $400 billion in lost productivity on\"}, {\"start\": 61.64, \"end\": 64.7, \"text\": \"the job.\"}, {\"start\": 64.7, \"end\": 70.28, \"text\": \"So if you've got a few extra minutes today, go ahead and knockout for a few minutes.\"}, {\"start\": 70.28, \"end\": 76.08, \"text\": \"Better still, try to get a good 8 to 10 hours of sleep tonight.\"}]"
  },
  "L9iHYHc-VFw": {
    "video_id": "L9iHYHc-VFw",
    "title": "Virginia and New York wooing Delta (ASL - 2.27.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180228",
    "duration": 109,
    "view_count": 84,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 2.3, \"end\": 11.2, \"text\": \"Last week, Delta Airlines joined several other companies by announcing it would no longer\"}, {\"start\": 11.2, \"end\": 16.34, \"text\": \"offer NRA members discounts following the school shooting in Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 16.34, \"end\": 27.08, \"text\": \"As a result, Georgia Republicans are threatening to kill part of a new bill that would eliminate\"}, {\"start\": 27.08, \"end\": 29.3, \"text\": \"a state tax for jet fuel.\"}, {\"start\": 29.3, \"end\": 40.16, \"text\": \"Georgia's Lt. Gov. Casey Cagle tweeted: \\\"I will kill any tax legislation that benefits\"}, {\"start\": 40.16, \"end\": 51.4, \"text\": \"Delta unless the company changes its position and fully reinstates its relationship with the NRA.\"}, {\"start\": 51.4, \"end\": 61.78, \"text\": \"Corporations cannot attack conservatives and expect us not to fight back.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 61.78, \"end\": 68.02, \"text\": \"Immediately lawmakers in Virginia and New York sent messages inviting Delta to move\"}, {\"start\": 68.02, \"end\": 72.58, \"text\": \"its headquarters to their states.\"}, {\"start\": 72.58, \"end\": 85.14, \"text\": \"On Twitter, Virginia's governor Ralph Northam wrote: \\\"Virginia is for lovers and airline hubs.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 85.14, \"end\": 88.56, \"text\": \"You're welcome here anytime.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 88.56, \"end\": 99.48, \"text\": \"New York Lt. Governor Kathy Hochul tweeted: \\\"Delta, as one of your most frequent flyers,\"}, {\"start\": 99.48, \"end\": 103.54, \"text\": \"know that the NYLG admires your principled stance.\"}, {\"start\": 103.54, \"end\": 107.34, \"text\": \"Move HQ to where you're appreciated.\\\"\"}]"
  },
  "5MUTjks5Dac": {
    "video_id": "5MUTjks5Dac",
    "title": "4.30.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180501",
    "duration": 531,
    "view_count": 1976,
    "description": "4.30.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Pence travels to border as migrant caravan reaches U.S.\n-Trump says he has damaging info on Top Democrat\n-Bill Cosby was never offered a flea deal\n-H.S. school student arrested for passing out pot brownies\n-World’s tallest geyser keeps erupting, scientists baffled\n-Pelicans attack Pepperdine graduation\n-Amazing photo: bird carries a shark carrying a fish\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talen",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.92, \"end\": 9.38, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.38, \"end\": 11.28, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.28, \"end\": 12.56, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.56, \"end\": 15.18, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.68, \"end\": 29.78, \"text\": \"Vice President Mike Pence traveled to the US/Mexico border today to look at the border\"}, {\"start\": 29.78, \"end\": 37.96, \"text\": \"wall in California, meet with border protection employees and to address the issue of the\"}, {\"start\": 37.96, \"end\": 41.7, \"text\": \"caravan of migrants seeking entry into the US.\"}, {\"start\": 41.7, \"end\": 51.5, \"text\": \"He praised the work of the border patrol agents and assured them the border wall will be completed\"}, {\"start\": 51.5, \"end\": 57.72, \"text\": \"to help stem the flow of illegal immigrants into the US from the South.\"}, {\"start\": 57.72, \"end\": 63.9, \"text\": \"Pence said since the border wall construction began, there has been significant decline\"}, {\"start\": 63.9, \"end\": 68.4, \"text\": \"in illegal border crossings in recent months.\"}, {\"start\": 68.4, \"end\": 73.54, \"text\": \"Meanwhile, hundreds of migrants are on the Mexican side of the border hoping to gain\"}, {\"start\": 73.54, \"end\": 75.26, \"text\": \"access into the country.\"}, {\"start\": 75.26, \"end\": 81.46, \"text\": \"They say they will stay there as long as it takes for their chance to meet with US officials\"}, {\"start\": 81.46, \"end\": 84.74, \"text\": \"to request asylum.\"}, {\"start\": 84.74, \"end\": 95.74, \"text\": \"US customs officials say they do not yet have the capacity to process their asylum claims.\"}, {\"start\": 95.74, \"end\": 102.04, \"text\": \"And even if they did, it would not guarantee entry into the US.\"}, {\"start\": 107.12, \"end\": 115.5, \"text\": \"While speaking at a rally in Michigan this weekend, President Trump said, quote, \\\"I know\"}, {\"start\": 115.5, \"end\": 120.56, \"text\": \"things about the senator I can say too.\"}, {\"start\": 120.56, \"end\": 124.36, \"text\": \"If I said them, he would never be re-elected again.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 124.36, \"end\": 132.74, \"text\": \"He was talking about Montana Senator Jon Tester.\"}, {\"start\": 132.74, \"end\": 140.48, \"text\": \"Tester is a top ranking Democrat on the Senate Veterans Affairs committee who released a\"}, {\"start\": 140.48, \"end\": 152.58, \"text\": \"scathing memo that documented questionable behavior by Dr. Ronny Jackson, Trump's pick\"}, {\"start\": 152.58, \"end\": 156.56, \"text\": \"to head the Veterans Affairs Administration.\"}, {\"start\": 156.56, \"end\": 160.04, \"text\": \"Jackson eventually withdrew himself for consideration for the job.\"}, {\"start\": 160.04, \"end\": 164.56, \"text\": \"After making his statements about Tester, Trump never offered any specifics about his\"}, {\"start\": 164.56, \"end\": 168.52, \"text\": \"claim of damaging information about the Senator.\"}, {\"start\": 168.52, \"end\": 172.42, \"text\": \"White House officials have not commented either.\"}, {\"start\": 175.26, \"end\": 191.58, \"text\": \"Last week a Pennsylvania jury found comedian Bill Cosby guilty of three counts of aggravated\"}, {\"start\": 191.58, \"end\": 194.62, \"text\": \"indecent assault against Andrea Constand.\"}, {\"start\": 194.62, \"end\": 204.24, \"text\": \"Now the prosecutor in the case is shooting down a newspaper report that Cosby turned\"}, {\"start\": 204.24, \"end\": 205.4, \"text\": \"down a plea deal.\"}, {\"start\": 205.4, \"end\": 210.4, \"text\": \"The New York Post Page 6 reports it spoke with Cosby and he said he refused to plead\"}, {\"start\": 210.4, \"end\": 217.14, \"text\": \"guilty under a deal offered last year.\"}, {\"start\": 217.16, \"end\": 222.12, \"text\": \"In response, a spokeswoman for the district attorney's office said the office has never\"}, {\"start\": 222.12, \"end\": 223.62, \"text\": \"offered a plea deal to Cosby.\"}, {\"start\": 223.62, \"end\": 228.72, \"text\": \"She says they were confident in their evidence and they were focused on proceeding to trial.\"}, {\"start\": 228.72, \"end\": 239.0, \"text\": \"Cosby's PR team is also shot down the report saying the interview with Page 6 never happened.\"}, {\"start\": 243.52, \"end\": 254.48, \"text\": \"A Michigan high school student could face charges for passing out marijuana brownies\"}, {\"start\": 254.48, \"end\": 257.82, \"text\": \"to her classmates.\"}, {\"start\": 257.82, \"end\": 265.54, \"text\": \"Police say some of the students became ill after eating the brownies.\"}, {\"start\": 265.54, \"end\": 272.16, \"text\": \"The 18-year-old female student was arrested shortly after the incident.\"}, {\"start\": 272.16, \"end\": 279.06, \"text\": \"She posted bond and was released from custody but the district attorney's office is still\"}, {\"start\": 279.06, \"end\": 283.4, \"text\": \"trying to determine if any criminal charges will be filed.\"}, {\"start\": 283.4, \"end\": 290.74, \"text\": \"The students who became ill were also cited for marijuana possession for violating the\"}, {\"start\": 290.74, \"end\": 297.9, \"text\": \"schools drug-free zone policy.\"}, {\"start\": 301.04, \"end\": 310.1, \"text\": \"The tallest active geyser in the world is at Yellowstone Park.\"}, {\"start\": 310.1, \"end\": 320.96, \"text\": \"It's called the \\\"steamboat geyser\\\" and it doesn't usually erupt that often -- until now.\"}, {\"start\": 320.98, \"end\": 327.74, \"text\": \"Scientists say it has erupted three times in the past six weeks and they don't know why.\"}, {\"start\": 327.74, \"end\": 334.52, \"text\": \"According to the US Geological survey, this is the first time the geyser has had multiple\"}, {\"start\": 334.52, \"end\": 339.16, \"text\": \"eruptions in a single year since 2003.\"}, {\"start\": 339.16, \"end\": 346.28, \"text\": \"The geyser's first eruption was on March 15, the second one took place on April 19 and\"}, {\"start\": 346.28, \"end\": 350.0, \"text\": \"the third and largest of the three eruptions occurred on Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 350.0, \"end\": 355.08, \"text\": \"Scientists are stumped about what's causing all the activity.\"}, {\"start\": 355.08, \"end\": 360.2, \"text\": \"It could be a new thermal disturbance or the geyser could merely be entering a period of\"}, {\"start\": 360.2, \"end\": 363.36, \"text\": \"more frequent eruptions.\"}, {\"start\": 363.36, \"end\": 367.6, \"text\": \"If you're hoping to try an catch eruption, your out of luck for now.\"}, {\"start\": 367.6, \"end\": 373.44, \"text\": \"This time of year the area of the park the steamboat geyser is in is closed to tourists\"}, {\"start\": 373.44, \"end\": 377.48, \"text\": \"until the snow melts.\"}, {\"start\": 379.76, \"end\": 391.71, \"text\": \"A pair of pelicans swooped down into the crowd of Pepperdine University's oceanside ceremony\"}, {\"start\": 391.72, \"end\": 394.72, \"text\": \"in Malibu on Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 394.72, \"end\": 397.56, \"text\": \"And no matter what people did to try to shoot them away, they stayed until they were good\"}, {\"start\": 397.56, \"end\": 401.68, \"text\": \"and ready to leave.\"}, {\"start\": 401.68, \"end\": 406.88, \"text\": \"In fact, one bird actually sat on someone's lap.\"}, {\"start\": 406.88, \"end\": 409.44, \"text\": \"And when a man tried to pick up one of the birds, the pelican sharply turned his head\"}, {\"start\": 409.44, \"end\": 411.48, \"text\": \"and took a bite.\"}, {\"start\": 411.48, \"end\": 413.0, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 443.72, \"end\": 449.84, \"text\": \"The pelicans eventually went on their way and the ceremony continued.\"}, {\"start\": 453.84, \"end\": 460.4, \"text\": \"A man recently took these images of an osprey with a fresh kill in its talons flying hundreds\"}, {\"start\": 460.4, \"end\": 467.48, \"text\": \"of feet in the air in Florida's Gulf Coast.\"}, {\"start\": 467.48, \"end\": 479.24, \"text\": \"He knew he got great shots but when he looked at them on his computer, they got even better.\"}, {\"start\": 479.24, \"end\": 487.0, \"text\": \"He noticed that the prey, which he thought was a fish, was in fact a small shark.\"}, {\"start\": 487.04, \"end\": 493.56, \"text\": \"Then he saw the shark also had prey clinched in its jaw -- a small fish.\"}, {\"start\": 493.56, \"end\": 496.2, \"text\": \"These are amazing photos!\"}, {\"start\": 496.2, \"end\": 503.92, \"text\": \"They've been shared thousands of times since being posted.\"}, {\"start\": 507.0, \"end\": 509.92, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 509.92, \"end\": 511.2, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 511.2, \"end\": 513.52, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 513.52, \"end\": 517.64, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 517.64, \"end\": 519.04, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 519.04, \"end\": 520.4, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 520.4, \"end\": 523.48, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "FwZtKAt4uiY": {
    "video_id": "FwZtKAt4uiY",
    "title": "Dr. G answers your questions: I'm older with health issues. Am I high risk for coronavirus?",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200422",
    "duration": 105,
    "view_count": 343,
    "description": "Posted 4.22.20",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en-US",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.98, \"end\": 8.6, \"text\": \"Many people worry because of age and the risk for getting this illness.\"}, {\"start\": 8.72, \"end\": 11.78, \"text\": \"I have a lot of different questions about that.\"}, {\"start\": 11.78, \"end\": 26.62, \"text\": \"Laura is concerned because she is almost 60 and her doctor says she has pneumonia and asthma.\"}, {\"start\": 26.62, \"end\": 36.34, \"text\": \"Another person says they are above 60 and worried about what to do.\"}, {\"start\": 36.34, \"end\": 40.42, \"text\": \"It's true age is a risk factor.\"}, {\"start\": 40.42, \"end\": 43.92, \"text\": \"If you're above 60, the risk is high.\"}, {\"start\": 43.92, \"end\": 47.84, \"text\": \"If you're above 70 the risk is higher.\"}, {\"start\": 47.84, \"end\": 52.64, \"text\": \"And if you're above 80 years old, that's the highest risk.\"}, {\"start\": 52.64, \"end\": 69.7, \"text\": \"Other illnesses like diabetes, lung disease, heart disease, immune system issues or medicines\"}, {\"start\": 69.7, \"end\": 81.3, \"text\": \"weaken your immune system all make you a higher risk for the illness.\"}, {\"start\": 81.3, \"end\": 87.74, \"text\": \"That means you have to be extra careful and not see other people who are not living with you.\"}, {\"start\": 87.74, \"end\": 94.02, \"text\": \"Maybe you can ask someone to go to grocery store for you, leave the food outside the\"}, {\"start\": 94.02, \"end\": 97.1, \"text\": \"door and pick it up later.\"}, {\"start\": 97.1, \"end\": 101.09, \"text\": \"Be sure to wash your hands thoroughly and continuously.\"}, {\"start\": 101.09, \"end\": 103.86, \"text\": \"That will help protect you.\"}]"
  },
  "aRaWoeDRc7s": {
    "video_id": "aRaWoeDRc7s",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.11.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180312",
    "duration": 402,
    "view_count": 1252,
    "description": "3.11.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Fox News host to divorce after affair with employe\n-Trump slams California in weekly address\n-Scott Baio’s wife reveals brain disease diagnosis\n-NFL player pulls Jeep to strength train\n-“Black Panther” crosses $1B less than one month\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.94, \"end\": 9.34, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.34, \"end\": 11.32, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.32, \"end\": 13.3, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 13.3, \"end\": 16.5, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.24, \"end\": 32.48, \"text\": \"According to the New York Daily Mail, popular Fox News host Jesse Watters' wife has filed\"}, {\"start\": 32.48, \"end\": 45.56, \"text\": \"for divorce after it was revealed the 39-year-old was having an affair with Emma DiGiovine,\"}, {\"start\": 45.56, \"end\": 49.24, \"text\": \"a 25-year-old associate producer of his show.\"}, {\"start\": 49.24, \"end\": 56.72, \"text\": \"Noelle Watters filed for divorce in October.\"}, {\"start\": 56.72, \"end\": 68.42, \"text\": \"Sources say Jesse Watters informed his bosses of the affair shortly thereafter.\"}, {\"start\": 68.42, \"end\": 71.366, \"text\": \"After news of the affair news of the affair\"}, {\"start\": 71.366, \"end\": 77.04, \"text\": \"became public, DiGiovine was transferred to another FOX show.\"}, {\"start\": 77.04, \"end\": 82.72, \"text\": \"Sources say Watters and DiGiovine are still dating.\"}, {\"start\": 86.72, \"end\": 95.16, \"text\": \"Earlier this week, the Trump administration announced plans to sue California over state\"}, {\"start\": 95.16, \"end\": 109.6, \"text\": \"laws that seek to shield undocumented immigrants from federal immigration authorities.\"}, {\"start\": 109.61, \"end\": 120.13, \"text\": \"President Trump slammed California for that policy during his weekly address Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 120.13, \"end\": 131.76, \"text\": \"He said the state of California is sheltering dangerous criminals in a brazen and lawless\"}, {\"start\": 131.76, \"end\": 137.04, \"text\": \"attack on our constitutional system of government.\"}, {\"start\": 137.04, \"end\": 145.4, \"text\": \"He said California's leaders are in open defiance of federal law and they don't care about crime,\"}, {\"start\": 145.4, \"end\": 150.68, \"text\": \"death, killings and robberies.\"}, {\"start\": 150.68, \"end\": 161.16, \"text\": \"Trump also went after Oakland Mayor Libby Schaaf, who recently issued a public warning\"}, {\"start\": 161.16, \"end\": 169.28, \"text\": \"to the city's undocumented immigrants about the possibility of an imminent federal crackdown.\"}, {\"start\": 169.28, \"end\": 175.88, \"text\": \"President Trump accused Schaaf of threatening the safety of federal immigration officers and\"}, {\"start\": 175.88, \"end\": 181.92, \"text\": \"law-abiding Americans with her remarks.\"}, {\"start\": 185.4, \"end\": 197.36, \"text\": \"Scott Baio and his wife Renee Sloan took to Twitter Saturday to confirm some sad news.\"}, {\"start\": 197.36, \"end\": 204.96, \"text\": \"Sloan was diagnosed with a brain disease in October 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 204.96, \"end\": 218.76, \"text\": \"The disease is a common condition that affects the blood vessels in the brain.\"}, {\"start\": 218.76, \"end\": 225.28, \"text\": \"Baio tweeted: \\\"Unfortunately this is true.\"}, {\"start\": 225.28, \"end\": 232.11, \"text\": \"Renee is forever my rock, my life and my soulmate.\"}, {\"start\": 232.11, \"end\": 235.5, \"text\": \"Toughest person I know.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 235.5, \"end\": 238.76, \"text\": \"This isn't Sloan's first health issue.\"}, {\"start\": 238.76, \"end\": 243.28, \"text\": \"She was diagnosed with a brain tumor in 2015.\"}, {\"start\": 245.44, \"end\": 259.16, \"text\": \"New Orleans Saints running back Alvin Kamara has one insane workout.\"}, {\"start\": 259.16, \"end\": 263.04, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 263.04, \"end\": 274.16, \"text\": \"Instead of doing squats to strengthen his legs, he pulls a Jeep!\"}, {\"start\": 274.16, \"end\": 283.96, \"text\": \"And he's holding up a weight rack with four plates on his shoulders.\"}, {\"start\": 283.96, \"end\": 290.68, \"text\": \"He walks about 20 yards and that's believed to burn 90,000 calories.\"}, {\"start\": 290.68, \"end\": 296.08, \"text\": \"It's insane but apparently it's working.\"}, {\"start\": 296.08, \"end\": 305.56, \"text\": \"Kamara was named the NFL's 2018 Offensive Rookie of the Year.\"}, {\"start\": 308.84, \"end\": 316.24, \"text\": \"The smash box office hit \\\"Black Panther\\\" has crossed the $1 billion mark at the global\"}, {\"start\": 316.24, \"end\": 317.92, \"text\": \"box office.\"}, {\"start\": 317.92, \"end\": 320.16, \"text\": \"That's right -- $1 billion!\"}, {\"start\": 320.32, \"end\": 325.08, \"text\": \"And the film has done it in less than a month.\"}, {\"start\": 325.08, \"end\": 340.68, \"text\": \"The Disney and Marvel studios film hit that number on his 26th day of release.\"}, {\"start\": 340.68, \"end\": 345.0, \"text\": \"And global sales are only going up.\"}, {\"start\": 345.0, \"end\": 357.12, \"text\": \"\\\"Black Panther\\\" opened in China Friday and made $22 million on his first day of release there.\"}, {\"start\": 357.12, \"end\": 362.52, \"text\": \"Only 33 movies have made $1 billion around the world.\"}, {\"start\": 362.52, \"end\": 366.48, \"text\": \"Now \\\"Black Panther\\\" is one of them.\"}, {\"start\": 366.48, \"end\": 374.96, \"text\": \"And it is now the seventh highest grossing film of all time in the US.\"}, {\"start\": 378.2, \"end\": 380.36, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 380.36, \"end\": 381.92, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 381.92, \"end\": 384.52, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 384.52, \"end\": 389.32, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 389.32, \"end\": 395.56, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "SYKqVhZdWk4": {
    "video_id": "SYKqVhZdWk4",
    "title": "Space-X PAZ mission launch (ASL - 2.22.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180223",
    "duration": 71,
    "view_count": 145,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.62, \"end\": 14.36, \"text\": \"A Space-X Falcon 9 rocket launched Thursday morning from California's Vandenberg Air Force Base.\"}, {\"start\": 14.36, \"end\": 25.66, \"text\": \"The primary mission is to deliver Spain's Paz satellite into low orbit.\"}, {\"start\": 25.66, \"end\": 31.92, \"text\": \"But the rocket also gets founder Elon Musk closer to his goal of providing high-speed\"}, {\"start\": 31.92, \"end\": 41.26, \"text\": \"internet to the world using thousands of tiny satellites.\"}, {\"start\": 41.26, \"end\": 49.7, \"text\": \"Along with the Paz satellite, the Falcon 9 rocket carried two experimental internet delivery\"}, {\"start\": 49.72, \"end\": 58.38, \"text\": \"satellites.\"}, {\"start\": 58.42, \"end\": 68.66, \"text\": \"Space-X will use them to test technology designed to beam high-speed internet to Earth's surface.\"}]"
  },
  "grkqUYcf68w": {
    "video_id": "grkqUYcf68w",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.8.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180309",
    "duration": 533,
    "view_count": 1155,
    "description": "3.8.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Update: GVRA cancels policy change on Gallaudet/NTID\n-Officer killed, sent to wrong address\n-Trump signs tariff order\n-Meghan Markle baptized in private ceremony\n-Your comments: 10-year old runs to school as punishment\n-Shelter pets enjoy donated furniture\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in America",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 9.38, \"end\": 10.5, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 10.5, \"end\": 12.5, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.5, \"end\": 14.04, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 14.04, \"end\": 17.18, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.06, \"end\": 35.36, \"text\": \"Yesterday we told you about the Georgia Vocational Rehabilitation Agency's proposed policy change\"}, {\"start\": 35.38, \"end\": 43.62, \"text\": \"that would have removed Gallaudet University and the National Technical Institute for the\"}, {\"start\": 43.62, \"end\": 45.86, \"text\": \"Deaf from its list of approved schools for college funding.\"}, {\"start\": 45.86, \"end\": 54.92, \"text\": \"The policy change would have impacted thousands of Deaf and hard-of-hearing students across\"}, {\"start\": 54.92, \"end\": 56.64, \"text\": \"the state.\"}, {\"start\": 56.64, \"end\": 63.32, \"text\": \"The Deaf community was prepared to show up in masses to protest the policy change.\"}, {\"start\": 63.32, \"end\": 74.04, \"text\": \"But today GVRA Executive Director Sean Casey released this statement.\"}, {\"start\": 74.04, \"end\": 81.05, \"text\": \"It says he has listened to the heartfelt concerns\"}, {\"start\": 81.05, \"end\": 84.04, \"text\": \"about the change.\"}, {\"start\": 84.04, \"end\": 90.38, \"text\": \"As a result Casey says he's revoking the proposed policy change effective immediately.\"}, {\"start\": 90.38, \"end\": 103.78, \"text\": \"This means every student currently enrolled at Gallaudet or NTID, plus future applicants,\"}, {\"start\": 103.78, \"end\": 106.08, \"text\": \"will have the opportunity to pursue their education with no changes to services and\"}, {\"start\": 106.08, \"end\": 108.06, \"text\": \"tuition assistance.\"}, {\"start\": 110.94, \"end\": 124.58, \"text\": \"On Tuesday police officer Christopher Morton was shot to death at a home in Clinton, Missouri.\"}, {\"start\": 124.58, \"end\": 133.82, \"text\": \"Morton and two other officers were sent to a home after receiving a 911 call.\"}, {\"start\": 133.82, \"end\": 144.06, \"text\": \"When they arrived, they encountered 37-year-old James Waters.\"}, {\"start\": 144.06, \"end\": 152.16, \"text\": \"Waters opened fire on the officers, killing Morton, then barricaded himself inside the home.\"}, {\"start\": 152.18, \"end\": 157.98, \"text\": \"When officers entered the home, they found Waters dead.\"}, {\"start\": 157.98, \"end\": 163.0, \"text\": \"Two other officers were injured but they are expected to be okay.\"}, {\"start\": 163.0, \"end\": 171.26, \"text\": \"Now investigators say the officers were sent to the wrong house.\"}, {\"start\": 171.26, \"end\": 179.04, \"text\": \"The Missouri Highway Patrol says the officers should not have been sent to the Clinton address\"}, {\"start\": 179.04, \"end\": 185.46, \"text\": \"because the 911 call originated from an address in nearby Windsor.\"}, {\"start\": 185.46, \"end\": 190.08, \"text\": \"MHP says Windsor is about 15 miles away from Clinton and the 911 request was somehow attached\"}, {\"start\": 190.08, \"end\": 192.6, \"text\": \"to the Clinton location.\"}, {\"start\": 192.6, \"end\": 197.12, \"text\": \"The address-tracing error will be investigated.\"}, {\"start\": 200.14, \"end\": 216.16, \"text\": \"Today President Trump signed an order to place new tariffs on imported steel and aluminum.\"}, {\"start\": 216.16, \"end\": 224.26, \"text\": \"The decision has sparked a debate, with some fully behind the decision and others in complete\"}, {\"start\": 224.32, \"end\": 225.92, \"text\": \"disagreement.\"}, {\"start\": 225.92, \"end\": 231.36, \"text\": \"The Steelworkers Union and businesses that financially benefit from steel and aluminum\"}, {\"start\": 231.36, \"end\": 233.84, \"text\": \"support the tax.\"}, {\"start\": 233.84, \"end\": 242.26, \"text\": \"Those against the idea say it will cause a trade war.\"}, {\"start\": 242.26, \"end\": 250.7, \"text\": \"One person that did not love this idea was the president's former chief economic advisor.\"}, {\"start\": 250.7, \"end\": 257.78, \"text\": \"Gary Cohen resigned this week in the wake of his disagreement with the plan.\"}, {\"start\": 257.78, \"end\": 266.92, \"text\": \"President Trump says the measures are needed to balance global trade deficits and defend\"}, {\"start\": 266.92, \"end\": 272.36, \"text\": \"America's national security.\"}, {\"start\": 272.36, \"end\": 280.64, \"text\": \"White House senior advisors say the president has been open-minded about the details and\"}, {\"start\": 280.64, \"end\": 287.74, \"text\": \"there's a chance some countries, like Canada and Mexico, will be exempt.\"}, {\"start\": 291.96, \"end\": 300.62, \"text\": \"Meghan Markle has been baptized into the Church of England.\"}, {\"start\": 300.62, \"end\": 313.36, \"text\": \"The Daily Mail reports the archbishop of Canterbury conducted a private ceremony in the Chapel\"}, {\"start\": 313.36, \"end\": 322.48, \"text\": \"Royal at St. James's Palace.\"}, {\"start\": 322.48, \"end\": 329.18, \"text\": \"It was not mandatory for Markle to convert to marry Prince Harry but she said she would\"}, {\"start\": 329.18, \"end\": 335.04, \"text\": \"do it before their wedding in May.\"}, {\"start\": 335.04, \"end\": 343.52, \"text\": \"Queen Elizabeth is the head of the Church of England.\"}, {\"start\": 343.52, \"end\": 351.3, \"text\": \"Markle attended a Roman Catholic high school but was brought up Protestant.\"}, {\"start\": 355.66, \"end\": 368.9, \"text\": \"Yesterday we told you about the 10-year-old boy whose father forced him to run 1 mile\"}, {\"start\": 368.9, \"end\": 379.1, \"text\": \"to school for three days as punishment for bullying his classmates on the school bus.\"}, {\"start\": 379.1, \"end\": 388.92, \"text\": \"We wanted to know if you thought the punishment was appropriate or too harsh.\"}, {\"start\": 388.92, \"end\": 391.92, \"text\": \"Here's what you had to say:\"}, {\"start\": 391.92, \"end\": 402.42, \"text\": \"Reynoldo Llarena said: \\\"I think this punishment is reasonable.\"}, {\"start\": 402.42, \"end\": 411.62, \"text\": \"Those kids who bully should be punished and have zero tolerance.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 411.62, \"end\": 421.44, \"text\": \"Donna Mosler said: \\\"I remember when I was young.\"}, {\"start\": 421.44, \"end\": 425.08, \"text\": \"I had a belt and hand on my bum.\"}, {\"start\": 425.08, \"end\": 435.36, \"text\": \"I learned lessons and I know what's wrong and what's right and if we don't teach our children\"}, {\"start\": 435.46, \"end\": 437.38, \"text\": \"like that, they will have trouble possibly.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 437.38, \"end\": 444.16, \"text\": \"Reynaldo and Donna, thank you for sharing your thoughts.\"}, {\"start\": 447.48, \"end\": 453.98, \"text\": \"Shelter dogs and cats are animals without a home.\"}, {\"start\": 453.98, \"end\": 465.58, \"text\": \"But the Knox County Humane Society in Illinois came up with the bright idea to make the animals\"}, {\"start\": 465.58, \"end\": 469.18, \"text\": \"feel right at home.\"}, {\"start\": 469.18, \"end\": 476.82, \"text\": \"They are asking people to donate old chairs so the animals will feel comfortable while\"}, {\"start\": 476.82, \"end\": 483.72, \"text\": \"they wait to meet potential owners.\"}, {\"start\": 483.72, \"end\": 485.86, \"text\": \"And it is working!\"}, {\"start\": 485.86, \"end\": 497.0, \"text\": \"A video posted to Facebook of the pets enjoying chairs racked up more than 14 million views.\"}, {\"start\": 497.0, \"end\": 503.48, \"text\": \"Since then donations have been rolling in from all over the country.\"}, {\"start\": 506.5, \"end\": 509.28, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 509.28, \"end\": 510.72, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 510.72, \"end\": 513.18, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 513.18, \"end\": 517.82, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 517.82, \"end\": 524.32, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-7AQlPgDPN0": {
    "video_id": "-7AQlPgDPN0",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.20.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20181221",
    "duration": 592,
    "view_count": 1675,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Senate votes to keep government open, Trump refuses to sign\n-Border wall GoFundMe  campaign raises millions\n-Trump plans to make people work for food stamps\n-Facebook let 150+ companies access users’ private data\n-Budweiser looking at making cannabis drinks\n-How the interest rate hike impacts you\n-Scared of losing your mind? Get moving\n-NASA engineer nabs porch pirates with GPS, glitter, fart spray",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 24.64, \"end\": 26.18, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 26.18, \"end\": 28.08, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 28.08, \"end\": 29.34, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 29.34, \"end\": 31.56, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 35.74, \"end\": 46.02, \"text\": \"Late last night the Senate passed a stopgap spending bill that would keep the government\"}, {\"start\": 46.02, \"end\": 49.22, \"text\": \"funded until early February.\"}, {\"start\": 49.22, \"end\": 58.42, \"text\": \"The measure now goes to the House where is likely to pass and then to the president's\"}, {\"start\": 58.42, \"end\": 60.94, \"text\": \"desk for his signature.\"}, {\"start\": 60.94, \"end\": 68.12, \"text\": \"But late this afternoon President Trump informed House Republicans that he refuses to sign\"}, {\"start\": 68.12, \"end\": 76.68, \"text\": \"the stopgap measure because lawmakers did not set aside $5 billion for his border wall construction.\"}, {\"start\": 76.68, \"end\": 84.54, \"text\": \"That means lawmakers are now scrambling to come up with another solution to keep funds\"}, {\"start\": 84.54, \"end\": 91.02, \"text\": \"flowing to some government agencies after Friday's shut down deadline passes.\"}, {\"start\": 94.62, \"end\": 102.82, \"text\": \"One Florida man may have a solution to Trump's border wall funding problem.\"}, {\"start\": 102.82, \"end\": 115.1, \"text\": \"37-year-old veteran Brian Kolfage has started a GoFundMe campaign to raise money for the wall.\"}, {\"start\": 115.1, \"end\": 118.06, \"text\": \"The account was created on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 118.06, \"end\": 123.92, \"text\": \"As of right now it is raised over $6 million.\"}, {\"start\": 123.92, \"end\": 127.3, \"text\": \"The goal is $1 billion.\"}, {\"start\": 127.3, \"end\": 132.58, \"text\": \"Kolfage says he made contact with the Trump administration and a legal firm to ensure\"}, {\"start\": 132.58, \"end\": 139.56, \"text\": \"that the government could not use the money for anything but a wall.\"}, {\"start\": 142.12, \"end\": 151.4, \"text\": \"The Trump administration wants to require anyone receiving food assistance to work.\"}, {\"start\": 151.4, \"end\": 159.18, \"text\": \"On Thursday the Department of Agriculture unveiled a proposed rule expanding work requirements\"}, {\"start\": 159.18, \"end\": 167.34, \"text\": \"for those in the supplemental nutrition assistance program or SNAP.\"}, {\"start\": 167.34, \"end\": 178.18, \"text\": \"SNAP already requires that non-disabled, working age adults, without dependents have jobs.\"}, {\"start\": 178.18, \"end\": 186.32, \"text\": \"If they aren't working or participating in training programs 20 hours a week, SNAP recipients\"}, {\"start\": 186.32, \"end\": 192.7, \"text\": \"can only get benefits for three months out of every 36 month period.\"}, {\"start\": 192.7, \"end\": 201.84, \"text\": \"But states can waive that requirement for areas where unemployment is at least 10 percent\"}, {\"start\": 201.84, \"end\": 204.58, \"text\": \"or there are not enough jobs.\"}, {\"start\": 204.58, \"end\": 211.64, \"text\": \"The new proposal would make it harder for states to receive those waivers and it tightens\"}, {\"start\": 211.64, \"end\": 215.5, \"text\": \"the definition of areas where there are insufficient jobs.\"}, {\"start\": 215.5, \"end\": 222.0, \"text\": \"Also in an unprecedented move, the administration has already started allowing states to require\"}, {\"start\": 222.0, \"end\": 226.98, \"text\": \"Medicaid recipients to work.\"}, {\"start\": 229.38, \"end\": 236.84, \"text\": \"A stunning investigation in the New York Times is detailing how Facebook shared private user\"}, {\"start\": 236.84, \"end\": 240.28, \"text\": \"information with dozens of companies.\"}, {\"start\": 240.28, \"end\": 248.74, \"text\": \"The Times says Facebook made deals with more than 150 companies.\"}, {\"start\": 248.74, \"end\": 257.96, \"text\": \"The investigation alleges Netflix and Spotify had the ability to read Facebook users' private\"}, {\"start\": 257.96, \"end\": 267.46, \"text\": \"messages, Amazon and Microsoft search engine could access the names of your Facebook friends\"}, {\"start\": 267.46, \"end\": 272.34, \"text\": \"and Yahoo could even look at your friends' posts.\"}, {\"start\": 272.34, \"end\": 276.54, \"text\": \"All without your consent.\"}, {\"start\": 276.54, \"end\": 283.08, \"text\": \"Netflix says it never asked for or accessed anyone's private messages.\"}, {\"start\": 283.08, \"end\": 289.22, \"text\": \"And several other companies also denied any wrongdoing.\"}, {\"start\": 292.6, \"end\": 300.88, \"text\": \"Budweiser wants you to be able to get your pot and beer in one drink!\"}, {\"start\": 300.88, \"end\": 308.26, \"text\": \"AB InBev, the parent company of Budweiser and the world's biggest brewer, says it will\"}, {\"start\": 308.26, \"end\": 315.98, \"text\": \"be teaming up with Canada's Tilray to research the possibilities.\"}, {\"start\": 315.98, \"end\": 323.86, \"text\": \"The two companies will invest a combined $100 million into the effort.\"}, {\"start\": 323.86, \"end\": 331.9, \"text\": \"Canada and several American states have legalized marijuana for recreational purposes.\"}, {\"start\": 331.9, \"end\": 341.84, \"text\": \"For now any drinks with cannabis ingredients can only be marketed in Canada.\"}, {\"start\": 341.84, \"end\": 351.52, \"text\": \"AB InBev will make a decision about whether cannabis-infused drinks are economically viable\"}, {\"start\": 351.52, \"end\": 353.1, \"text\": \"at a later date.\"}, {\"start\": 355.34, \"end\": 363.4, \"text\": \"If you save, invest, use credit or want to buy a house or car, listen up!\"}, {\"start\": 363.4, \"end\": 371.84, \"text\": \"The Federal Reserve's recent interest rate hike will impact just about everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 371.84, \"end\": 377.54, \"text\": \"The increase is by a quarter of a percentage point to a range of 2.25 to 2.5 percent.\"}, {\"start\": 377.54, \"end\": 380.56, \"text\": \"Here's how it could impact you.\"}, {\"start\": 380.56, \"end\": 389.24, \"text\": \"For borrowers it's going to cost more for credit cards, loans and mortgages.\"}, {\"start\": 389.24, \"end\": 394.56, \"text\": \"Experts say credit card users will feel the effects first.\"}, {\"start\": 394.56, \"end\": 402.92, \"text\": \"Depending on how much you owe that could mean an increase in your minimum payment.\"}, {\"start\": 402.92, \"end\": 407.36, \"text\": \"For savers it's good news.\"}, {\"start\": 407.36, \"end\": 415.8, \"text\": \"Experts say this latest hike will translate into more earnings on deposits in a savings account.\"}, {\"start\": 415.8, \"end\": 420.92, \"text\": \"However despite the increase, federal interest rates are still at historically low levels.\"}, {\"start\": 423.64, \"end\": 431.0, \"text\": \"If you are worried about how getting older will impact your ability to think, health\"}, {\"start\": 431.02, \"end\": 436.34, \"text\": \"experts say there could be one simple solution -- exercise.\"}, {\"start\": 436.34, \"end\": 444.94, \"text\": \"According to new research published in the journal Neurology, walking or cycling just\"}, {\"start\": 444.94, \"end\": 449.98, \"text\": \"three times a week can improve your brain function.\"}, {\"start\": 449.98, \"end\": 458.2, \"text\": \"Adding a heart-healthy diet can help seriously improve executive thinking skills.\"}, {\"start\": 458.2, \"end\": 465.58, \"text\": \"Over six months, health experts studied different groups of adults around the age of 65.\"}, {\"start\": 465.58, \"end\": 470.32, \"text\": \"All ate different diets and worked out on different regimens.\"}, {\"start\": 470.32, \"end\": 478.84, \"text\": \"The results showed that people who exercise more and ate healthier reversed their brain's\"}, {\"start\": 478.84, \"end\": 481.1, \"text\": \"aging by nine years.\"}, {\"start\": 481.1, \"end\": 486.28, \"text\": \"Unfortunately their memories didn't improve.\"}, {\"start\": 489.7, \"end\": 503.14, \"text\": \"Mark Rober, a former NASA engineer, had enough of porch pirates stealing packages from his front door.\"}, {\"start\": 503.14, \"end\": 512.18, \"text\": \"So he constructed a device complete with a pound of glitter, global positioning sensors,\"}, {\"start\": 512.18, \"end\": 520.64, \"text\": \"multiple cameras and potent fart spray - all in an attempt to shame anyone who was stealing\"}, {\"start\": 520.64, \"end\": 522.46, \"text\": \"from him.\"}, {\"start\": 522.46, \"end\": 531.36, \"text\": \"Rober posted a video of the thieves opening the packages in cars or at home.\"}, {\"start\": 531.36, \"end\": 535.64, \"text\": \"When the package was opened the thief would get covered in glitter and five bursts of fart\"}, {\"start\": 535.64, \"end\": 538.86, \"text\": \"spray every 30 seconds.\"}, {\"start\": 538.86, \"end\": 545.18, \"text\": \"And Rober says the thieves are in such a hurry, they fail to realize the package was sent\"}, {\"start\": 545.18, \"end\": 559.78, \"text\": \"by his childhood hero, Kevin McAllister, actor Macauley Culkin's character in the movie \\\"Home Alone.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 559.78, \"end\": 565.1, \"text\": \"No surprise, the video has gone viral with over 37 million views.\"}, {\"start\": 569.0, \"end\": 571.02, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 571.02, \"end\": 572.34, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 572.34, \"end\": 574.4, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 574.4, \"end\": 578.04, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 578.04, \"end\": 579.32, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 579.32, \"end\": 580.32, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 580.46, \"end\": 583.92, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "txkb931Vq4M": {
    "video_id": "txkb931Vq4M",
    "title": "“Bomb Cyclone” hammering the East Coast (ASL - 1.4.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180105",
    "duration": 83,
    "view_count": 285,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.94, \"end\": 10.28, \"text\": \"Every East Coast state from Maine to Florida is under some type of winter storm watch or\"}, {\"start\": 10.28, \"end\": 15.3, \"text\": \"warning.\"}, {\"start\": 15.3, \"end\": 22.44, \"text\": \"And meteorologists expect it to stay that way for the rest of the week.\"}, {\"start\": 22.44, \"end\": 30.7, \"text\": \"This weather pattern is called a \\\"bomb cyclone\\\" and forecasters say it isn't letting up anytime\"}, {\"start\": 30.7, \"end\": 32.38, \"text\": \"soon.\"}, {\"start\": 32.38, \"end\": 38.86, \"text\": \"The East Coast is being hit with freezing rain, sleet, snow, hurricane-force winds and\"}, {\"start\": 38.86, \"end\": 41.2, \"text\": \"some wintry mix combinations.\"}, {\"start\": 41.2, \"end\": 48.66, \"text\": \"At least 16 people have died this week due to severe weather.\"}, {\"start\": 48.7, \"end\": 59.06, \"text\": \"Across the region governors are urging people to stay inside and stay off the slick roads.\"}, {\"start\": 59.14, \"end\": 67.24, \"text\": \"Flights have been grounded, schools closed and grocery store shelves are empty.\"}, {\"start\": 67.24, \"end\": 73.76, \"text\": \"Unfortunately, for many states, the worst is still to come.\"}, {\"start\": 73.76, \"end\": 81.7, \"text\": \"By the end of this week, parts of the Northeast will be colder than Mars.\"}]"
  },
  "-_oUXqM2Zjc": {
    "video_id": "-_oUXqM2Zjc",
    "title": "Sign1News 9.29.19 - News for the Deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20190930",
    "duration": 779,
    "view_count": 1621,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n\n-Jethro shares your words of encouragement\n-Update: More teens face gang assault charges in stabbing\n-Santa Barbara Zoo euthanizes its last elephant\n-Another Legionnaires outbreak\n-First Republican supports impeachment inquiry\n-Rare early blizzard slams Montana\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national n",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 31.58, \"end\": 33.16, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 33.16, \"end\": 34.94, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 34.94, \"end\": 36.2, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 36.32, \"end\": 40.08, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 43.3, \"end\": 48.26, \"text\": \"As many of you know, a month ago I made the decision to focus on my health by losing weight.\"}, {\"start\": 48.26, \"end\": 54.08, \"text\": \"I stopped drinking sodas and I started drinking more water and walking.\"}, {\"start\": 54.1, \"end\": 59.98, \"text\": \"When my leg and foot started hurting, I was stuck and had to figure out what to do.\"}, {\"start\": 59.98, \"end\": 67.1, \"text\": \"That's when I found this picture which reminds me to be patient.\"}, {\"start\": 67.1, \"end\": 70.9, \"text\": \"It shows two lines of a silhouette of a man.\"}, {\"start\": 70.9, \"end\": 77.34, \"text\": \"On the first line, the silhouettes are getting progressively fatter.\"}, {\"start\": 77.34, \"end\": 84.22, \"text\": \"The caption under it reads: \\\"Took you 10 to 20 years to get here\\\" and there's a big blue\"}, {\"start\": 84.22, \"end\": 86.44, \"text\": \"arrow pointing to a fat silhouette at the end.\"}, {\"start\": 86.44, \"end\": 91.98, \"text\": \"On the second line, the silhouettes are getting progressively thinner and the caption under\"}, {\"start\": 91.98, \"end\": 99.94, \"text\": \"it reads: \\\"Stop expecting to get here in 30 days!\\\" and there's a big blue arrow pointing\"}, {\"start\": 99.94, \"end\": 102.46, \"text\": \"to a thin silhouette at the end.\"}, {\"start\": 102.46, \"end\": 108.28, \"text\": \"As many of you know, it can be a bit scary putting your personal life and private struggles\"}, {\"start\": 108.28, \"end\": 112.38, \"text\": \"on display for everyone to see.\"}, {\"start\": 112.38, \"end\": 119.84, \"text\": \"Nowadays people use social media like target practice to hurl hurtful words.\"}, {\"start\": 119.84, \"end\": 128.2, \"text\": \"But I gotta tell you, I have received nothing but positive feedback from you our loyal Sign1News\"}, {\"start\": 128.38, \"end\": 129.62, \"text\": \"viewers.\"}, {\"start\": 129.62, \"end\": 131.66, \"text\": \"I thank you for that.\"}, {\"start\": 131.66, \"end\": 137.72, \"text\": \"In fact, let me share some of your weight loss stories and words of encouragement.\"}, {\"start\": 140.8, \"end\": 150.74, \"text\": \"Michelle Mary Schaefer says \\\"It took me about four years I believe to lose 100 pounds. That's\"}, {\"start\": 150.84, \"end\": 156.84, \"text\": \"all just focusing on what I'm eating. But of course it wasn't 100 percent strict on\"}, {\"start\": 156.84, \"end\": 159.7, \"text\": \"healthy food. I believe in you.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 162.82, \"end\": 171.76, \"text\": \"ZA Hadrion says \\\"Sometimes it's the small changes that wrought the big differences.\"}, {\"start\": 171.76, \"end\": 175.38, \"text\": \"Keep it up Jethro and soon you will be able to do more with the strength you are gaining\"}, {\"start\": 175.38, \"end\": 178.34, \"text\": \"in the process.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 181.7, \"end\": 190.18, \"text\": \"Susan Marietta Jones says \\\"Nothing in life happens overnight. Just got to follow your\"}, {\"start\": 190.18, \"end\": 202.02, \"text\": \"routine and work really hard to achieve what you desire. You can do it!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 202.04, \"end\": 211.36, \"text\": \"And Priscilla Eberhardt said \\\"Congrats and stay positive and stay on your path, reach\"}, {\"start\": 211.36, \"end\": 217.04, \"text\": \"your best goal. We love you and I continue to support you Jethro!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 217.04, \"end\": 218.94, \"text\": \"Thank you everyone!\"}, {\"start\": 222.72, \"end\": 226.66, \"text\": \"We have an update to a story we brought you two weeks ago.\"}, {\"start\": 226.66, \"end\": 237.92, \"text\": \"Police say eighteen-year-old Tyler Flach stabbed sixteen-year-old Kahseen Morris multiple times\"}, {\"start\": 237.92, \"end\": 242.3, \"text\": \"in the chest.\"}, {\"start\": 242.3, \"end\": 249.32, \"text\": \"However according to police, the fight involved nearly 50 teens who planned and likely targeted\"}, {\"start\": 249.32, \"end\": 254.04, \"text\": \"Morris as a result of an ongoing dispute over a girl.\"}, {\"start\": 254.04, \"end\": 257.72, \"text\": \"Morris was taken to the hospital where he later died.\"}, {\"start\": 257.72, \"end\": 263.9, \"text\": \"The fatal ambush was witnessed by dozens and shared on Snapchat.\"}, {\"start\": 263.9, \"end\": 273.14, \"text\": \"Flach was arrested and pleaded not guilty to manslaughter charges.\"}, {\"start\": 273.14, \"end\": 279.64, \"text\": \"But on Saturday, just as Morris' family was laying him to rest, authorities announced\"}, {\"start\": 279.64, \"end\": 286.06, \"text\": \"seven more people will be facing charges in connection with the brutal attack.\"}, {\"start\": 286.08, \"end\": 294.3, \"text\": \"Five are teens who are being charged as adults and two others are being charged as juveniles\"}, {\"start\": 294.3, \"end\": 296.64, \"text\": \"and have not been identified.\"}, {\"start\": 296.64, \"end\": 302.1, \"text\": \"All seven face charges of gang assault.\"}, {\"start\": 302.1, \"end\": 309.72, \"text\": \"Police say more people could face charges as the investigation continues.\"}, {\"start\": 313.98, \"end\": 323.88, \"text\": \"In California, the Santa Barbara zoo says its last elephant was euthanized after a series\"}, {\"start\": 323.88, \"end\": 325.58, \"text\": \"of health issues.\"}, {\"start\": 325.58, \"end\": 335.08, \"text\": \"The zoo says Little Mac, a forty-eight-year-old Asian elephant, died Wednesday at her exhibit\"}, {\"start\": 335.08, \"end\": 343.6, \"text\": \"yard surrounded by keepers and other zoo workers who cared for her over the years.\"}, {\"start\": 343.6, \"end\": 352.18, \"text\": \"After two weeks of sharply declining health, the zoo decided to enter Little Mac into hospice\"}, {\"start\": 352.18, \"end\": 356.18, \"text\": \"care several days before her death.\"}, {\"start\": 356.18, \"end\": 361.92, \"text\": \"Litte Mac's mate Sujatha was euthanized nearly a year ago, also due to health issues related\"}, {\"start\": 361.92, \"end\": 364.64, \"text\": \"to old age.\"}, {\"start\": 364.64, \"end\": 372.74, \"text\": \"A zoo spokeswoman said Little Mac was the last elephant the zoo will ever have.\"}, {\"start\": 372.74, \"end\": 380.09, \"text\": \"That's because recent regulations require far more room than the zoo, so the zoo's elephant\"}, {\"start\": 380.09, \"end\": 387.52, \"text\": \"program and exhibit will be permanently closed.\"}, {\"start\": 387.52, \"end\": 396.66, \"text\": \"Little Mac's name, by the way, is a play on words on McDonald's Big Mac.\"}, {\"start\": 396.66, \"end\": 403.78, \"text\": \"The owner of several McDonald's locations in Santa Barbara paid for Little Mac and Sujatha\"}, {\"start\": 403.78, \"end\": 408.92, \"text\": \"to fly in from India and got the naming rights for one of them.\"}, {\"start\": 412.8, \"end\": 423.76, \"text\": \"Last month we told you about the deadly outbreak of Legionnaires' disease at a Sheraton Atlanta hotel.\"}, {\"start\": 423.76, \"end\": 427.6, \"text\": \"One person died from the disease and eleven other cases were confirmed.\"}, {\"start\": 427.6, \"end\": 434.16, \"text\": \"It was the largest Legionella outbreak in Georgia history.\"}, {\"start\": 434.16, \"end\": 440.64, \"text\": \"Now a second deadly outbreak of the disease struck the southeastern United States.\"}, {\"start\": 440.64, \"end\": 447.56, \"text\": \"The North Carolina Department of Public Health says at least one person has died and forty-two\"}, {\"start\": 447.56, \"end\": 451.16, \"text\": \"others have been hospitalized.\"}, {\"start\": 451.16, \"end\": 463.54, \"text\": \"This outbreak appears linked to water rides at the North Carolina mountain state fair in Fletcher.\"}, {\"start\": 463.54, \"end\": 473.92, \"text\": \"According to the CDC, the rate has increased across the US 550 percent since 2000.\"}, {\"start\": 473.92, \"end\": 483.34, \"text\": \"And they suspect the outbreak could be worse than they know because it can be difficult\"}, {\"start\": 483.34, \"end\": 485.6, \"text\": \"to diagnose the disease.\"}, {\"start\": 485.6, \"end\": 492.5, \"text\": \"The disease is a serious lung infection caused by the Legionella bacteria, typically found\"}, {\"start\": 492.5, \"end\": 501.64, \"text\": \"in warm freshwater like hot tubs, hot water tanks and decorative fountains.\"}, {\"start\": 501.64, \"end\": 507.74, \"text\": \"It can also be found in showerheads and plumbing systems in large building.\"}, {\"start\": 507.74, \"end\": 518.38, \"text\": \"Symptoms include severe coughing, muscle aches, fever, shortness of breath and headaches.\"}, {\"start\": 518.38, \"end\": 524.62, \"text\": \"It can typically be treated with antibiotics but people over the age of 50, those with\"}, {\"start\": 524.62, \"end\": 529.42, \"text\": \"weakened lungs or weakened immune systems are at a greater risk.\"}, {\"start\": 529.42, \"end\": 538.22, \"text\": \"According to a 2015 CDC report, about one in ten people affected with Legionnaires dies.\"}, {\"start\": 538.22, \"end\": 542.72, \"text\": \"So what is causing the increase in cases?\"}, {\"start\": 542.72, \"end\": 549.08, \"text\": \"Health experts believe it's a combination of people being more aware of the symptoms\"}, {\"start\": 549.08, \"end\": 558.12, \"text\": \"and seeking treatment, and the increase in building plumbing systems that have been neglected\"}, {\"start\": 558.12, \"end\": 559.7, \"text\": \"and not properly maintained.\"}, {\"start\": 565.42, \"end\": 578.3, \"text\": \"Nevada Congressman Mark Amodei is now the first Republican supporting an impeachment\"}, {\"start\": 578.3, \"end\": 580.96, \"text\": \"inquiry into President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 580.96, \"end\": 590.38, \"text\": \"But to be clear, Amodei says he supports an inquiry but not impeachment itself.\"}, {\"start\": 590.38, \"end\": 599.12, \"text\": \"More than half the Democratically controlled House supports an impeachment investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 599.14, \"end\": 610.14, \"text\": \"A majority of the House needs to vote to impeach the President to send the process to the Republican-\"}, {\"start\": 610.14, \"end\": 613.64, \"text\": \"controlled Senate were it would likely go nowhere.\"}, {\"start\": 613.86, \"end\": 623.02, \"text\": \"There has been a surge in support for launching an inquiry amid a growing controversy over\"}, {\"start\": 623.02, \"end\": 632.5, \"text\": \"Trump's phone call with Ukraine's president in which he discussed former Vice President Joe Biden.\"}, {\"start\": 632.5, \"end\": 634.72, \"text\": \"Trump denies doing anything improper.\"}, {\"start\": 639.12, \"end\": 648.28, \"text\": \"It's barely even fall but it feels more like the heart of winter in parts of Montana.\"}, {\"start\": 648.28, \"end\": 654.1, \"text\": \"More than a foot of snow has fallen since a historic winter storm impacted the region.\"}, {\"start\": 654.1, \"end\": 662.1, \"text\": \"It happened when a cold front with strong winds moved in followed by a low pressure system.\"}, {\"start\": 662.1, \"end\": 666.78, \"text\": \"All that cold air made sure the precipitation that fell was frozen leading to significant\"}, {\"start\": 666.78, \"end\": 668.34, \"text\": \"snow accumulation.\"}, {\"start\": 668.34, \"end\": 678.96, \"text\": \"Strong winds near tropical storm strength are producing white out conditions in some\"}, {\"start\": 678.96, \"end\": 682.46, \"text\": \"regions of the northern Rockies.\"}, {\"start\": 682.46, \"end\": 693.56, \"text\": \"Forecasters also warned those gusts could create waves as high 6 feet on Flathead Lake.\"}, {\"start\": 693.56, \"end\": 703.08, \"text\": \"Meanwhile cities like Dallas and Phoenix are still experiencing highs in the 90s.\"}, {\"start\": 706.02, \"end\": 707.86, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 707.86, \"end\": 709.66, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 709.66, \"end\": 711.88, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 711.88, \"end\": 719.96, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our app too.\"}, {\"start\": 719.96, \"end\": 725.1, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "hlyhPDsnnP4": {
    "video_id": "hlyhPDsnnP4",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.25.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180126",
    "duration": 460,
    "view_count": 1080,
    "description": "1.25.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Russell Simons accused of rape\n-A new plan to help Puerto Rico\n-Home Depot giving workers $1K bonuses\n-India Bollywood film controversy\n-Fewer young adults getting HIV test\n-Super Bowl fan rivalries are getting heated\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides eq",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.84, \"end\": 8.82, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.82, \"end\": 11.08, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.08, \"end\": 12.4, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.4, \"end\": 15.68, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.12, \"end\": 26.96, \"text\": \"Another woman has accused Russell Simmons, the founder of hip-hop music label DEF Jam\"}, {\"start\": 26.96, \"end\": 27.68, \"text\": \"Recordings, of rape.\"}, {\"start\": 27.68, \"end\": 30.44, \"text\": \"Simmons stepped down from his companies last November after a woman accused him of forcing\"}, {\"start\": 30.44, \"end\": 33.2, \"text\": \"her to have sex with him in 1991.\"}, {\"start\": 33.2, \"end\": 36.16, \"text\": \"Simmons denies the allegations.\"}, {\"start\": 36.24, \"end\": 45.92, \"text\": \"On Wednesday a 5-million dollar federal lawsuit was filed in Los Angeles.\"}, {\"start\": 45.92, \"end\": 56.72, \"text\": \"In 2016, filmmaker Jennifer Jarosik says Simmons used a possible business venture as an excuse\"}, {\"start\": 56.72, \"end\": 58.96, \"text\": \"to assault her.\"}, {\"start\": 58.96, \"end\": 62.4, \"text\": \"Jarosik says Simmons invited her to his LA home to discuss her film, then he attacked\"}, {\"start\": 62.4, \"end\": 64.56, \"text\": \"and raped her.\"}, {\"start\": 64.56, \"end\": 68.48, \"text\": \"Simmons was never charged in the alleged incident.\"}, {\"start\": 68.48, \"end\": 76.8, \"text\": \"Jarosik is asking for compensation for the alleged sexual assault and battery, intentional\"}, {\"start\": 76.8, \"end\": 84.56, \"text\": \"infliction of emotional distress and negligent infliction of emotional distress.\"}, {\"start\": 84.56, \"end\": 88.48, \"text\": \"Simmons called Jarosik’s allegations absolutely untrue.\"}, {\"start\": 88.48, \"end\": 93.76, \"text\": \"In response, Jarosik’s attorney says his client also intends to pursue criminal charges\"}, {\"start\": 93.76, \"end\": 95.44, \"text\": \"against Simmons.\"}, {\"start\": 97.84, \"end\": 104.08, \"text\": \"In September Hurricane Maria struck Puerto Rico, leaving the island’s infrastructure\"}, {\"start\": 104.08, \"end\": 109.04, \"text\": \"and power grid crippled.\"}, {\"start\": 109.2, \"end\": 117.76, \"text\": \"New York Senator Kirsten Gillibrand is calling on lawmakers to do more to help Puerto Rico\"}, {\"start\": 117.76, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"recover from the devastation left by the storm.\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 129.52, \"text\": \"The island’s power authority says electricity has been restored to more than 1 million customers,\"}, {\"start\": 129.52, \"end\": 135.28, \"text\": \"450,000 people remain without power.\"}, {\"start\": 135.52, \"end\": 143.76, \"text\": \"Gillibrand warned against losing sight of the island’s urgent, ongoing need for help.\"}, {\"start\": 143.76, \"end\": 149.76, \"text\": \"The devastation in Puerto Rico has also impacted the island’s continuing debt crisis.\"}, {\"start\": 149.76, \"end\": 157.76, \"text\": \"According to the New York Times, Puerto Rican officials say the island will not be able\"}, {\"start\": 157.76, \"end\": 161.44, \"text\": \"to pay down any of its massive debt for the next five years.\"}, {\"start\": 163.76, \"end\": 173.2, \"text\": \"Home Depot is paying $1,000 bonuses to its hourly employees.\"}, {\"start\": 173.2, \"end\": 177.36, \"text\": \"Home Depot says they are able to do this because of the recent tax reform.\"}, {\"start\": 177.36, \"end\": 181.44, \"text\": \"The bonus amounts will be based on how long the employee has worked for the company.\"}, {\"start\": 181.44, \"end\": 185.68, \"text\": \"All of Home Depot’s hourly employees will get at least $200.\"}, {\"start\": 185.68, \"end\": 189.12, \"text\": \"The maximum payout is $1,000 for employees that have worked for the company for 20 years\"}, {\"start\": 189.12, \"end\": 191.28, \"text\": \"or more.\"}, {\"start\": 191.28, \"end\": 203.84, \"text\": \"Other companies giving their employees bonuses include Disney, Starbucks and Walmart.\"}, {\"start\": 206.72, \"end\": 214.0, \"text\": \"In India, many people want to watch a controversial Bollywood film, but violent protests over\"}, {\"start\": 214.0, \"end\": 225.76, \"text\": \"its release haven’t stopped.\"}, {\"start\": 225.76, \"end\": 231.92, \"text\": \"The producers of “Padmaavat” have delayed its release over fears for the safety of its\"}, {\"start\": 232.08, \"end\": 241.6, \"text\": \"female star following death threats from prominent Hindu protesters.\"}, {\"start\": 241.6, \"end\": 250.24, \"text\": \"The protesters are upset with the film’s rumored depiction of a romantic dream sequence\"}, {\"start\": 250.24, \"end\": 259.92, \"text\": \"involving a mythical Hindu queen and an invading Muslim sultan.\"}, {\"start\": 260.24, \"end\": 266.0, \"text\": \"The filmmakers repeatedly denied the movie includes such a scene.\"}, {\"start\": 266.0, \"end\": 276.48, \"text\": \"Top leaders of protesting groups have been arrested to prevent a further escalation of\"}, {\"start\": 277.04, \"end\": 279.52, \"text\": \"violence.\"}, {\"start\": 282.32, \"end\": 291.2, \"text\": \"A new study published by the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) national health\"}, {\"start\": 291.2, \"end\": 298.72, \"text\": \"statistics says fewer young adults are getting tested for HIV.\"}, {\"start\": 298.72, \"end\": 310.48, \"text\": \"Almost 39 percent of women and 54 percent of men ages 15 to 44 say they have never been\"}, {\"start\": 310.48, \"end\": 320.8, \"text\": \"tested for HIV outside of donating blood or blood products between 2011 and 2015.\"}, {\"start\": 320.8, \"end\": 327.84, \"text\": \"That percentage escalated among the group ages 15 to 24 to almost 64 percent of women\"}, {\"start\": 328.16, \"end\": 333.12, \"text\": \"and 74 perent of men who reported never being tested.\"}, {\"start\": 333.12, \"end\": 337.68, \"text\": \"The most common reason they reported not getting tested is because they believed they were\"}, {\"start\": 337.68, \"end\": 340.96, \"text\": \"unlikely to been exposed to HIV.\"}, {\"start\": 340.96, \"end\": 350.0, \"text\": \"According to the CDC, roughly 166,000 of more than 1 million people in United States who\"}, {\"start\": 350.32, \"end\": 354.4, \"text\": \"are HIV-positive are not aware of their HIV status.\"}, {\"start\": 354.4, \"end\": 364.48, \"text\": \"Forty percent of new HIV infections are transmitted by people whose HIV remains undiagnosed.\"}, {\"start\": 364.56, \"end\": 369.84, \"text\": \"Doctors recommend testing for anyone who has had sex.\"}, {\"start\": 372.32, \"end\": 392.0, \"text\": \"Super Bowl preparations are ramping up in Minneapolis and fan rivalries are heating\"}, {\"start\": 392.0, \"end\": 394.72, \"text\": \"up in Philadelphia and Boston.\"}, {\"start\": 394.72, \"end\": 405.68, \"text\": \"A Philadelphia doughnut shop is banning all Boston cream donuts.\"}, {\"start\": 405.68, \"end\": 417.2, \"text\": \"Boston responded by banning all Philadelphia-related items from Esplanade Park, including Philly\"}, {\"start\": 417.2, \"end\": 425.2, \"text\": \"sportswear, cheesesteaks and cream cheese.\"}, {\"start\": 425.2, \"end\": 430.32, \"text\": \"The ban also prohibits bald eagles from loitering in the park.\"}, {\"start\": 433.52, \"end\": 436.4, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 436.4, \"end\": 437.92, \"text\": \"I’m Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 437.92, \"end\": 440.16, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 440.16, \"end\": 445.2, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 445.36, \"end\": 452.56, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "WeY6Uge23ao": {
    "video_id": "WeY6Uge23ao",
    "title": "Trump returns to D.C. with big “TO-DO” list (ASL - 1.2.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180103",
    "duration": 92,
    "view_count": 52,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.8, \"end\": 7.82, \"text\": \"President Trump is back in Washington after 10 days of vacation.\"}, {\"start\": 7.82, \"end\": 12.98, \"text\": \"He starts a new year with a number of challenges on his plate.\"}, {\"start\": 12.98, \"end\": 21.72, \"text\": \"The first: a January 19th deadline to pass a spending bill and avert a government shutdown\"}, {\"start\": 21.72, \"end\": 26.18, \"text\": \"that could cost billions.\"}, {\"start\": 26.18, \"end\": 33.3, \"text\": \"The government is set to run out of money on January 19th and a spending solution is going\"}, {\"start\": 33.3, \"end\": 38.9, \"text\": \"to have to come from both sides of the aisle.\"}, {\"start\": 38.9, \"end\": 47.16, \"text\": \"Another issue that will be the front and center: protection for so-called \\\"dreamers\\\" who\"}, {\"start\": 47.16, \"end\": 54.34, \"text\": \"were brought to the country illegally as children.\"}, {\"start\": 54.34, \"end\": 63.06, \"text\": \"The president insists that there will not be a deal on DACA without funding for the wall he\"}, {\"start\": 63.06, \"end\": 66.74, \"text\": \"wants to build along the US-Mexico border.\"}, {\"start\": 66.74, \"end\": 71.06, \"text\": \"Democrats are already saying \\\"no deal.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 71.06, \"end\": 82.48, \"text\": \"As for the rest of the legislative agenda, President Trump is expecting to meet with Senate majority leader\"}, {\"start\": 82.48, \"end\": 91.68, \"text\": \"Mitch McConnell and House Speaker Paul Ryan this weekend at Camp David to hash out some of the details.\"}]"
  },
  "eivBB7B6hVA": {
    "video_id": "eivBB7B6hVA",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.10.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180310",
    "duration": 540,
    "view_count": 1164,
    "description": "3.10.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Gunman identified in veterans home hostage standoff\n-Teen charged in deadly shooting at Birmingham HS\n-Florida passes historic gun law\n-NRA sues Florida\n-White House scolds cabinet members\n-Reminder: clocks spring forward one hour\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1New",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.98, \"end\": 10.1, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 10.1, \"end\": 12.66, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.7, \"end\": 14.36, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 14.36, \"end\": 18.3, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.6, \"end\": 30.7, \"text\": \"Police say three people were killed at a military veterans home in Northern California on Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 30.7, \"end\": 45.3, \"text\": \"Police say 36-year-old Albert Wong barged into a going away party with a rifle and started\"}, {\"start\": 45.3, \"end\": 47.57, \"text\": \"shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 47.57, \"end\": 53.74, \"text\": \"Dozens of law-enforcement officials responded to the 911 calls.\"}, {\"start\": 53.74, \"end\": 64.0, \"text\": \"Wong refused to leave the facility and held several people hostage.\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 75.6, \"text\": \"After six hours of negotiating, police eventually stormed into the room.\"}, {\"start\": 75.6, \"end\": 81.28, \"text\": \"They found Wong and three hostages dead.\"}, {\"start\": 81.28, \"end\": 90.22, \"text\": \"Police later learned Wong was a former patient at the facility.\"}, {\"start\": 90.22, \"end\": 92.6, \"text\": \"He left two weeks ago.\"}, {\"start\": 92.6, \"end\": 101.16, \"text\": \"Authorities have not given a motive for Wong's actions.\"}, {\"start\": 104.54, \"end\": 112.98, \"text\": \"We have an update on a story we first told you about earlier this week on Facebook live.\"}, {\"start\": 112.98, \"end\": 122.88, \"text\": \"On Wednesday, two shots rang out Hoffman high school in Birmingham, Alabama.\"}, {\"start\": 122.88, \"end\": 128.64, \"text\": \"One student was killed, another injured.\"}, {\"start\": 128.64, \"end\": 135.59, \"text\": \"Investigators initially said the shooting was an accident.\"}, {\"start\": 135.59, \"end\": 151.6, \"text\": \"Police have now charged 17-year-old Michael Barber with manslaughter.\"}, {\"start\": 151.6, \"end\": 163.96, \"text\": \"After reviewing video of the shooting and interviewing students, the charges were upgraded\"}, {\"start\": 163.96, \"end\": 165.74, \"text\": \"to manslaughter.\"}, {\"start\": 165.74, \"end\": 172.02, \"text\": \"Prosecutors say Barber will be tried as an adult.\"}, {\"start\": 172.02, \"end\": 183.54, \"text\": \"The incident was the 14th school shooting in the US this year.\"}, {\"start\": 186.12, \"end\": 191.94, \"text\": \"Three weeks after the Florida high school massacre, the state passed gun-control restrictions\"}, {\"start\": 191.94, \"end\": 193.8, \"text\": \"into law.\"}, {\"start\": 193.8, \"end\": 198.6, \"text\": \"Under the new law you must be 21 to buy a gun.\"}, {\"start\": 198.6, \"end\": 208.54, \"text\": \"Buying or possessing bump stocks is illegal.\"}, {\"start\": 208.54, \"end\": 217.72, \"text\": \"And law enforcement has more power to seize weapons and ammunition from those deemed mentally\"}, {\"start\": 217.72, \"end\": 221.08, \"text\": \"unfit.\"}, {\"start\": 221.08, \"end\": 227.34, \"text\": \"A controversial portion of the law allows some teachers to be armed but only if the\"}, {\"start\": 227.34, \"end\": 236.66, \"text\": \"local school district and Sheriff's Department agree.\"}, {\"start\": 236.66, \"end\": 246.62, \"text\": \"What isn't included in the legislation is an assault weapons ban.\"}, {\"start\": 246.62, \"end\": 254.36, \"text\": \"The law is named after the school where a 19-year-old opened fire and killed 17 people:\"}, {\"start\": 254.36, \"end\": 258.64, \"text\": \"Marjory Stoneman Douglas high school.\"}, {\"start\": 260.32, \"end\": 270.96, \"text\": \"The National Rifle Association isn't happy with the new gun laws.\"}, {\"start\": 270.96, \"end\": 281.04, \"text\": \"A few hours after the Florida gun law passed, the NRA filed a federal lawsuit to block it.\"}, {\"start\": 281.04, \"end\": 290.8, \"text\": \"The lawsuit argues the law violates the constitutional rights of Florida adults who have not yet\"}, {\"start\": 290.88, \"end\": 293.94, \"text\": \"turned 21.\"}, {\"start\": 293.94, \"end\": 309.02, \"text\": \"Officials with the NRA said the bill punishes law abiding gun owners for the criminal acts\"}, {\"start\": 309.02, \"end\": 311.56, \"text\": \"of one deranged individual.\"}, {\"start\": 313.56, \"end\": 326.08, \"text\": \"White House Chief of Staff John Kelly reportedly slapped the hands of several cabinet officials\"}, {\"start\": 326.08, \"end\": 332.92, \"text\": \"after negative stories were reported about them in the press.\"}, {\"start\": 332.92, \"end\": 349.82, \"text\": \"They are Interior Secretary Ryan Zinke, Housing and Urban Development (HUD) Secretary Ben\"}, {\"start\": 349.82, \"end\": 363.58, \"text\": \"Carson, Veterans Administration (VA) Secretary David Shulkin and Environmental Protection\"}, {\"start\": 363.58, \"end\": 367.06, \"text\": \"Agency administrator Scott Pruitt.\"}, {\"start\": 367.06, \"end\": 382.08, \"text\": \"They have all made headlines recently for money issues\"}, {\"start\": 382.08, \"end\": 395.88, \"text\": \"including first-class travel, expensive office furniture and internal strife within their\"}, {\"start\": 395.9, \"end\": 397.88, \"text\": \"departments.\"}, {\"start\": 397.88, \"end\": 415.2, \"text\": \"Kelly instructed them to keep records that can prove their innocence in the face of complaints\"}, {\"start\": 415.2, \"end\": 428.54, \"text\": \"and to understand that just because an action is legal doesn't mean it looks good to the public.\"}, {\"start\": 431.92, \"end\": 438.26, \"text\": \"Don't forget to set your clocks ahead one hour tonight.\"}, {\"start\": 438.26, \"end\": 448.28, \"text\": \"The good news: the sun will set later so people will enjoy more daylight hours.\"}, {\"start\": 448.28, \"end\": 451.58, \"text\": \"The bad news: we will lose one hour of sleep.\"}, {\"start\": 451.58, \"end\": 459.06, \"text\": \"Losing one hour may not seem like much, but that small change can be a big deal for your health.\"}, {\"start\": 459.1, \"end\": 464.54, \"text\": \"According to the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) many people aren't getting\"}, {\"start\": 464.54, \"end\": 466.38, \"text\": \"enough sleep to begin with.\"}, {\"start\": 466.38, \"end\": 471.76, \"text\": \"And losing another hour can lead to deadly consequences.\"}, {\"start\": 471.76, \"end\": 479.72, \"text\": \"According to a Stanford University study, the Monday after the timeshift is linked to\"}, {\"start\": 479.72, \"end\": 483.1, \"text\": \"an increase in tragic car accidents.\"}, {\"start\": 483.1, \"end\": 492.34, \"text\": \"Also adults who miss out on even one hour of sleep a day are more likely to report health\"}, {\"start\": 492.34, \"end\": 497.16, \"text\": \"problems like diabetes, depression and heart disease.\"}, {\"start\": 497.16, \"end\": 505.02, \"text\": \"Experts suggest you use the time change to reset your sleep habits to make sure you get\"}, {\"start\": 505.02, \"end\": 507.52, \"text\": \"enough rest.\"}, {\"start\": 510.76, \"end\": 513.98, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 514.1, \"end\": 515.3, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 515.38, \"end\": 518.52, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 518.52, \"end\": 524.3, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 524.3, \"end\": 531.28, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "Qt_mjM3HFBA": {
    "video_id": "Qt_mjM3HFBA",
    "title": "Your comments: 10-year old runs to school as punishment (ASL - 3.8.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180309",
    "duration": 90,
    "view_count": 261,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.46, \"end\": 14.08, \"text\": \"Yesterday we told you about the 10-year-old boy whose father forced him to run 1 mile\"}, {\"start\": 14.08, \"end\": 24.82, \"text\": \"to school for three days as punishment for bullying his classmates on the school bus.\"}, {\"start\": 24.82, \"end\": 34.88, \"text\": \"We wanted to know if you thought the punishment was appropriate or too harsh.\"}, {\"start\": 34.88, \"end\": 37.7, \"text\": \"Here's what you had to say:\"}, {\"start\": 37.7, \"end\": 48.24, \"text\": \"Reynoldo Llarena said: \\\"I think this punishment is reasonable.\"}, {\"start\": 48.24, \"end\": 57.4, \"text\": \"Those kids who bully should be punished and have zero tolerance.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 57.4, \"end\": 66.08, \"text\": \"Donna Mosler said: \\\"I remember when I was young.\"}, {\"start\": 66.08, \"end\": 70.46, \"text\": \"I had a belt and hand on my bum.\"}, {\"start\": 70.46, \"end\": 76.13, \"text\": \"I learned lessons and I know what's wrong and what's right and if we don't teach our children\"}, {\"start\": 76.13, \"end\": 82.9, \"text\": \"like that, they will have trouble possibly.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 82.9, \"end\": 89.18, \"text\": \"Reynaldo and Donna, thank you for sharing your thoughts.\"}]"
  },
  "ZRu5_9uLGpM": {
    "video_id": "ZRu5_9uLGpM",
    "title": "5.22.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180523",
    "duration": 608,
    "view_count": 1066,
    "description": "5.22.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Congrats Julian Moiwai! Chubbies 1st Deaf Male Model\n-Attorney in viral rant offers apology, says he's not racist\n-Trump says June 12th meeting with N. Korea may be delayed\n-Teen charged as adult in death of police officer\n-Dozens hospitalized from synthetic marijuana\n-Hundreds attend \"BBQuing while black\" event\n-Sneak Peak at upcoming Hollywood movies\n-Dog adopts abandoned ducklings\n\nTHE ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.32, \"end\": 7.86, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.86, \"end\": 9.32, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.32, \"end\": 11.32, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.32, \"end\": 14.08, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.08, \"end\": 21.96, \"text\": \"Congratulations to Julian \\\"Juju\\\" Moiwai!\"}, {\"start\": 21.96, \"end\": 31.96, \"text\": \"Thanks to your votes he is the first Deaf man to be a Chubbies model.\"}, {\"start\": 31.96, \"end\": 39.16, \"text\": \"Moiwai received a two-year contract and free Chubbies apparel for life.\"}, {\"start\": 39.16, \"end\": 48.56, \"text\": \"He will now join 10 other winners from diverse backgrounds to promote the brand all over\"}, {\"start\": 48.56, \"end\": 49.64, \"text\": \"the world.\"}, {\"start\": 49.64, \"end\": 57.72, \"text\": \"On his Facebook page Moiwai says he is grateful for all of the support, love and encouragement\"}, {\"start\": 57.72, \"end\": 64.6, \"text\": \"you showed him and he looks forward to using his platform to represent deaf thighs.\"}, {\"start\": 64.6, \"end\": 70.92, \"text\": \"He also plans to vlog about his experience and share his Chubbies journey.\"}, {\"start\": 70.92, \"end\": 78.56, \"text\": \"Julian, from all of us here at Sign1News, congratulations!\"}, {\"start\": 78.56, \"end\": 88.04, \"text\": \"If you missed our interview with Julian last week, just head to our Facebook page and check it out.\"}, {\"start\": 88.04, \"end\": 92.68, \"text\": \"Julian, again, congratulations.\"}, {\"start\": 94.72, \"end\": 98.84, \"text\": \"Today Aaron Schlossberg issued an apology and said he is not a racist.\"}, {\"start\": 98.84, \"end\": 101.88, \"text\": \"Schlossberg is the attorney who was recorded screaming at customers and employees in a New York\"}, {\"start\": 101.88, \"end\": 110.16, \"text\": \"café because they were speaking Spanish.\"}, {\"start\": 110.16, \"end\": 113.12, \"text\": \"The video went viral.\"}, {\"start\": 113.12, \"end\": 125.84, \"text\": \"Schlossberg posted a message on Twitter and LinkedIn saying he is deeply sorry for his\"}, {\"start\": 125.84, \"end\": 130.4, \"text\": \"actions and he apologized to the people he insulted.\"}, {\"start\": 130.4, \"end\": 134.08, \"text\": \"But the apology may be too late.\"}, {\"start\": 134.08, \"end\": 142.72, \"text\": \"Political leaders in New York have filed complaint seeking to have Schlossberg's law license suspended.\"}, {\"start\": 142.72, \"end\": 148.64, \"text\": \"And the company that operates a center where Schlossberg law office is located have already\"}, {\"start\": 148.64, \"end\": 153.36, \"text\": \"terminated his lease.\"}, {\"start\": 154.48, \"end\": 163.6, \"text\": \"South Korean President Moon Jae-In traveled to Washington, DC today for a sitdown meeting\"}, {\"start\": 163.6, \"end\": 166.48, \"text\": \"with President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 166.48, \"end\": 175.52, \"text\": \"They were going to discuss next month's planned summit in Singapore between the US and North Korea.\"}, {\"start\": 175.52, \"end\": 181.04, \"text\": \"That summit now appears to be on shaky ground.\"}, {\"start\": 181.04, \"end\": 185.36, \"text\": \"Trump said there is a very substantial chance the meeting won't happen.\"}, {\"start\": 185.36, \"end\": 189.92, \"text\": \"But he added that doesn't mean it won't happen at a later date.\"}, {\"start\": 189.92, \"end\": 197.52, \"text\": \"And there are new reports that Trump has some reservations about holding the meeting.\"}, {\"start\": 197.52, \"end\": 203.68, \"text\": \"Last week North Korea threatened to withdraw from the meeting because of military drills\"}, {\"start\": 203.68, \"end\": 210.16, \"text\": \"that were being conducted between the US and South Korea, drills that were planned many\"}, {\"start\": 210.16, \"end\": 217.28, \"text\": \"months prior to the Korean peace talks.\"}, {\"start\": 220.32, \"end\": 229.28, \"text\": \"Authorities have charged 16-year-old Dawnta Anthony in the death of Baltimore County officer\"}, {\"start\": 229.28, \"end\": 235.12, \"text\": \"Amy Caprio.\"}, {\"start\": 235.12, \"end\": 243.52, \"text\": \"Prosecutors say he will be charged as an adult with first-degree murder.\"}, {\"start\": 243.52, \"end\": 247.04, \"text\": \"Anthony is accused of hitting Caprio with his car Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 247.04, \"end\": 254.32, \"text\": \"The 29-year-old officer died at the hospital from her injuries.\"}, {\"start\": 254.32, \"end\": 261.2, \"text\": \"According to court documents Anthony admitted he drove at the officer.\"}, {\"start\": 261.2, \"end\": 267.44, \"text\": \"The documents report Anthony said he was waiting in the vehicle as people he was with committed\"}, {\"start\": 267.44, \"end\": 269.68, \"text\": \"burglary.\"}, {\"start\": 269.68, \"end\": 272.96, \"text\": \"Three other teens have been charged in connection in the case.\"}, {\"start\": 272.96, \"end\": 279.04, \"text\": \"Those teens are suspects in burglaries in the area.\"}, {\"start\": 281.44, \"end\": 290.72, \"text\": \"There is a batch of especially toxic synthetic marijuana making the rounds in New York City.\"}, {\"start\": 290.72, \"end\": 301.6, \"text\": \"Over the past two days, the NYPD says it has arrested 13 people for selling K2.\"}, {\"start\": 301.6, \"end\": 309.04, \"text\": \"At least 49 overdoses have been reported at five separate locations.\"}, {\"start\": 309.04, \"end\": 320.24, \"text\": \"Authorities say K2 is always dangerous and potentially deadly but the strain going around\"}, {\"start\": 320.24, \"end\": 322.48, \"text\": \"is severely threatening.\"}, {\"start\": 322.48, \"end\": 332.56, \"text\": \"The police hope the recent arrests will lead to the specific source of the K2 distribution.\"}, {\"start\": 332.56, \"end\": 340.8, \"text\": \"Residents are advised to contact 911 immediately if they think they see someone who is overdosing\"}, {\"start\": 340.8, \"end\": 343.12, \"text\": \"on K2.\"}, {\"start\": 344.88, \"end\": 353.12, \"text\": \"On Sunday a community in Oakland, California held an event that was dubbed \\\"Barbecuing\"}, {\"start\": 353.12, \"end\": 362.72, \"text\": \"While Black\\\" in response to a woman's controversial call to police in April.\"}, {\"start\": 362.72, \"end\": 370.32, \"text\": \"Hundreds showed up for the Sunday cookout which featured music, dancing and appearances\"}, {\"start\": 370.32, \"end\": 375.84, \"text\": \"by local African-American political candidates.\"}, {\"start\": 375.84, \"end\": 379.28, \"text\": \"But it wasn't just a chance to have fun.\"}, {\"start\": 379.28, \"end\": 382.48, \"text\": \"It was a good-natured protest.\"}, {\"start\": 382.48, \"end\": 392.0, \"text\": \"The idea started after a white woman called police on a group of African-American people\"}, {\"start\": 392.0, \"end\": 392.96, \"text\": \"in April.\"}, {\"start\": 392.96, \"end\": 399.44, \"text\": \"She said they were using a charcoal grill in an area where it was banned.\"}, {\"start\": 399.44, \"end\": 408.44, \"text\": \"No one was arrested but video of the incident went viral and sparked outrage.\"}, {\"start\": 408.44, \"end\": 415.08, \"text\": \"It was seen as another instance of white people calling 911 on black people for seemingly\"}, {\"start\": 415.08, \"end\": 417.56, \"text\": \"trivial reasons.\"}, {\"start\": 418.76, \"end\": 426.36, \"text\": \"Here's a sneak peek at some big Hollywood movies coming out soon.\"}, {\"start\": 426.36, \"end\": 431.0, \"text\": \"\\\"City of Lies\\\" is coming in September.\"}, {\"start\": 431.0, \"end\": 442.56, \"text\": \"It stars Forrest Whitaker as a journalist and Johnny Depp as a detective.\"}, {\"start\": 442.56, \"end\": 449.56, \"text\": \"They team up to crack the conspiracy surrounding the infamously unsolved murder of the rapper\"}, {\"start\": 449.56, \"end\": 461.0, \"text\": \"legend Christopher Wallace, a.k.a. Biggie Smalls.\"}, {\"start\": 461.0, \"end\": 472.48, \"text\": \"Keanu Reeves is returning as the assassin John Wick in the movie \\\"John Wick: Chapter 3.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 472.48, \"end\": 481.96, \"text\": \"This time he'll be co-starring with Oscar-winning actress Halle Berry.\"}, {\"start\": 481.96, \"end\": 489.04, \"text\": \"No word on her role but sources say she is not the villain.\"}, {\"start\": 489.04, \"end\": 494.56, \"text\": \"Berry confirmed the news on Twitter, saying \\\"See you in a year\\\" and added the movie release\"}, {\"start\": 494.56, \"end\": 499.64, \"text\": \"date: May 17, 2019.\"}, {\"start\": 499.64, \"end\": 505.56, \"text\": \"It's been 35 years since Scarface first blazed across the big screen.\"}, {\"start\": 505.56, \"end\": 515.0, \"text\": \"To mark the anniversary, the gangster film is getting a re-release in 200 US theaters\"}, {\"start\": 515.0, \"end\": 516.8, \"text\": \"on June 10.\"}, {\"start\": 516.8, \"end\": 529.08, \"text\": \"After that, audiences will get a bonus: They'll get to see a conversation with director Brian\"}, {\"start\": 529.08, \"end\": 536.0, \"text\": \"de Palma and the film's stars, recorded at the Tribeca film Festival in April.\"}, {\"start\": 537.84, \"end\": 542.84, \"text\": \"A dog named Fred has become a foster father\"}, {\"start\": 542.84, \"end\": 545.08, \"text\": \"to nine abandoned ducklings.\"}, {\"start\": 545.08, \"end\": 555.6, \"text\": \"The Labrador lives at Mountfitchet Castle, a tourist attraction near London.\"}, {\"start\": 555.6, \"end\": 560.36, \"text\": \"The ducklings were found abandoned after their mother disappeared.\"}, {\"start\": 560.36, \"end\": 567.08, \"text\": \"Ten-year-old Fred quickly stepped up and has been babysitting ever since.\"}, {\"start\": 567.08, \"end\": 572.4, \"text\": \"No surprise, the internet is loving it!\"}, {\"start\": 572.4, \"end\": 581.72, \"text\": \"Fred has become an overnight sensation thanks to his puppy love for his furry friends.\"}, {\"start\": 583.96, \"end\": 586.48, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 586.48, \"end\": 588.04, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 588.04, \"end\": 589.72, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 589.72, \"end\": 594.24, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 594.24, \"end\": 595.76, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 595.76, \"end\": 596.76, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 596.76, \"end\": 600.64, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "1O97jR0Pwd0": {
    "video_id": "1O97jR0Pwd0",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.24.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180224",
    "duration": 506,
    "view_count": 1061,
    "description": "2.24.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-9-1-1 calls reveal Florida shooter’s troubled life\n-More companies cutting ties with the NRA\n-Waymo wants to prevent vomiting in self-driving cars\n-Tiffany Haddish to host MTV Movie and TV Awards\n-Massive demand for “Black Panther” in Kenya\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Languag",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.46, \"end\": 8.5, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.5, \"end\": 10.14, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.14, \"end\": 12.04, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.04, \"end\": 14.5, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.9, \"end\": 28.64, \"text\": \"In the days since the massacre at Marjory Stoneman Douglas high school, more information\"}, {\"start\": 28.64, \"end\": 35.34, \"text\": \"is coming out about the shooter Nikolas Cruz.\"}, {\"start\": 35.34, \"end\": 41.14, \"text\": \"Newly released 911 calls reveal a troubled young man who was often\"}, {\"start\": 41.14, \"end\": 44.4, \"text\": \"at odds with law enforcement.\"}, {\"start\": 44.44, \"end\": 52.68, \"text\": \"From 2008 to 2016, there were at least 39 calls for service at Cruz's home.\"}, {\"start\": 52.68, \"end\": 56.68, \"text\": \"Many of the calls were made by Cruz's mother.\"}, {\"start\": 56.68, \"end\": 65.98, \"text\": \"Additional calls came from other family members he stayed with following her death last November.\"}, {\"start\": 65.98, \"end\": 71.54, \"text\": \"Here is the transcript of one of those 911 calls:\"}, {\"start\": 71.54, \"end\": 74.68, \"text\": \"\\\"911 emergency how can I help you?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 74.68, \"end\": 79.14, \"text\": \"\\\"Yeah there was a fight in my house a kid and my son.\"}, {\"start\": 79.14, \"end\": 86.32, \"text\": \"I need someone here because I'm afraid he comes back and he has a lot of weapons.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 86.32, \"end\": 89.4, \"text\": \"\\\"What kind of weapon ma'am?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 89.4, \"end\": 91.1, \"text\": \"\\\"Let me ask my son.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 91.1, \"end\": 93.78, \"text\": \"\\\"What kind of weapon did he get?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 93.78, \"end\": 96.4, \"text\": \"\\\"A Remington.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 96.4, \"end\": 100.04, \"text\": \"\\\"Oh... and who did this?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 100.04, \"end\": 103.96, \"text\": \"\\\"Nikolas Cruz.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 103.96, \"end\": 112.96, \"text\": \"As Cruz got older his behavior became more alarming.\"}, {\"start\": 112.96, \"end\": 121.5, \"text\": \"Callers told 911 dispatchers they were scared he would hurt them or himself, especially once\"}, {\"start\": 121.5, \"end\": 125.14, \"text\": \"he was old enough to purchase weapons.\"}, {\"start\": 125.14, \"end\": 131.06, \"text\": \"Here's a transcript from another 911 call:\"}, {\"start\": 131.06, \"end\": 137.16, \"text\": \"\\\"He also dug in the backyard because he knew he was not allowed to bring it here and we\"}, {\"start\": 137.16, \"end\": 138.42, \"text\": \"found that he did.\"}, {\"start\": 138.42, \"end\": 141.2, \"text\": \"He was going to bury the gun there.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 141.2, \"end\": 148.12, \"text\": \"Then last month another call came, this time to the FBI tip line.\"}, {\"start\": 148.12, \"end\": 158.46, \"text\": \"A woman close to Cruz called saying she feared Cruz was at a breaking point and worried about\"}, {\"start\": 158.46, \"end\": 163.98, \"text\": \"him getting into a school and just shooting the place up.\"}, {\"start\": 163.98, \"end\": 169.12, \"text\": \"The FBI later admitted it failed to investigate that tip.\"}, {\"start\": 171.98, \"end\": 178.84, \"text\": \"The number of companies cutting ties with the National Rifle Association (NRA) continues\"}, {\"start\": 178.84, \"end\": 183.06, \"text\": \"to grow.\"}, {\"start\": 183.06, \"end\": 189.1, \"text\": \"The latest companies are Delta and United Airlines.\"}, {\"start\": 189.1, \"end\": 192.82, \"text\": \"Both companies announced they are no longer offering discounted rates to NRA members and\"}, {\"start\": 192.82, \"end\": 199.04, \"text\": \"Delta has requested that the NRA remove its information from their website.\"}, {\"start\": 199.05, \"end\": 205.37, \"text\": \"\\\"True Car\\\" announced on Twitter that it will end its car buying service relationship with\"}, {\"start\": 205.37, \"end\": 212.48, \"text\": \"the NRA at the end of this month.\"}, {\"start\": 212.48, \"end\": 218.36, \"text\": \"After the school shooting in Florida last week, many people demanded stronger gun laws.\"}, {\"start\": 218.36, \"end\": 226.82, \"text\": \"NRA supporters disagreed. As a result many companies ended their partnerships with the organization.\"}, {\"start\": 226.82, \"end\": 238.56, \"text\": \"Several rental companies including Enterprise, Hertz and Avis, say they are ending discount\"}, {\"start\": 238.56, \"end\": 241.66, \"text\": \"programs with the NRA.\"}, {\"start\": 241.74, \"end\": 251.22, \"text\": \"Insurance giant MetLife will no longer offer home and auto policy discounts for NRA members.\"}, {\"start\": 251.22, \"end\": 261.2, \"text\": \"And the First National Bank of Omaha is pledging to no longer issue NRA-branded Visa cards.\"}, {\"start\": 261.2, \"end\": 270.06, \"text\": \"The bank says it made his decision due to what it called \\\"customer feedback\\\" but did\"}, {\"start\": 270.06, \"end\": 272.12, \"text\": \"not elaborate.\"}, {\"start\": 275.5, \"end\": 283.54, \"text\": \"Waymo, the company behind a self-driving car project,\"}, {\"start\": 283.54, \"end\": 291.18, \"text\": \"says it has the technology that will prevent motion sickness in its vehicles.\"}, {\"start\": 291.18, \"end\": 304.98, \"text\": \"The technology would choose routes without stop-and-go traffic to spare motion-sensitive\"}, {\"start\": 304.98, \"end\": 307.48, \"text\": \"passengers.\"}, {\"start\": 307.48, \"end\": 315.68, \"text\": \"It would also reduce sudden acceleration and back-and-forth swaying of the vehicle.\"}, {\"start\": 315.68, \"end\": 326.4, \"text\": \"On top of that, self-driving cars would tell sensitive passengers which seat to take to\"}, {\"start\": 326.4, \"end\": 328.6, \"text\": \"minimize motion sickness.\"}, {\"start\": 328.6, \"end\": 335.38, \"text\": \"Waymo is applying for a patent related to the new technology.\"}, {\"start\": 335.38, \"end\": 343.8, \"text\": \"The company plans to launch a public self-driving service in Arizona later this year.\"}, {\"start\": 347.24, \"end\": 357.94, \"text\": \"Comedian Tiffany Haddish announced Friday on Instagram that she will host the 2018 MTV\"}, {\"start\": 357.94, \"end\": 361.1, \"text\": \"movie and TV awards.\"}, {\"start\": 361.1, \"end\": 364.58, \"text\": \"The show will air on June 18th.\"}, {\"start\": 364.58, \"end\": 370.46, \"text\": \"This latest honor just adds to Haddish's already growing list of accomplishments.\"}, {\"start\": 370.46, \"end\": 379.18, \"text\": \"In 2017 she starred in the award-winning movie \\\"Girl's Trip.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 379.18, \"end\": 393.12, \"text\": \"Her book, \\\"The Last Black Unicorn,\\\" was a New York Times bestseller and she premiered\"}, {\"start\": 393.12, \"end\": 399.96, \"text\": \"a new stand-up special on Showtime.\"}, {\"start\": 399.96, \"end\": 409.18, \"text\": \"She's also set to star in shows on CBS and Netflix as well as in Universal's movie \\\"Night\"}, {\"start\": 409.18, \"end\": 411.2, \"text\": \"School.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 414.7, \"end\": 425.38, \"text\": \"The movie \\\"Black Panther\\\" is being embraced by audiences in Nairobi, Kenya like no other\"}, {\"start\": 425.38, \"end\": 428.28, \"text\": \"movie before it.\"}, {\"start\": 428.28, \"end\": 438.66, \"text\": \"Theaters are having to make room because demand is through the roof, especially for the young\"}, {\"start\": 438.68, \"end\": 440.48, \"text\": \"fans.\"}, {\"start\": 440.48, \"end\": 450.64, \"text\": \"One woman started a crowd funding campaign to get a group of 200 teenagers to see the\"}, {\"start\": 450.64, \"end\": 452.54, \"text\": \"movie in 3-D.\"}, {\"start\": 452.6, \"end\": 457.76, \"text\": \"She raised $2,000 in just 24 hours.\"}, {\"start\": 457.76, \"end\": 464.52, \"text\": \"For many young people, it was their first movie theater experience.\"}, {\"start\": 464.52, \"end\": 474.74, \"text\": \"For others, the movie is about identity, about who they are and being proud to see other\"}, {\"start\": 474.74, \"end\": 479.1, \"text\": \"black people being celebrated on the big screen.\"}, {\"start\": 481.46, \"end\": 483.52, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 483.52, \"end\": 485.12, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 485.12, \"end\": 487.2, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 487.2, \"end\": 491.4, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 491.4, \"end\": 496.86, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "l1_ttFLvHWk": {
    "video_id": "l1_ttFLvHWk",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.24.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180325",
    "duration": 923,
    "view_count": 1486,
    "description": "3.24.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-\"March for our lives\" rallies around the world\n-MLK Jr's granddaughter speaks to protestors in DC\n-Groundhog wanted by police \n-Apple pushes for emojis to represent disabilities\n-Deaf hip hop artist Sean Forbes performs in Atlanta\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.64, \"end\": 8.66, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.66, \"end\": 10.66, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.66, \"end\": 12.24, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.34, \"end\": 15.28, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.96, \"end\": 23.62, \"text\": \"Millions of protesters around the country and the world came together for the massive\"}, {\"start\": 23.72, \"end\": 26.52, \"text\": \"\\\"March For Our Lives\\\" demonstrations Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 28.0, \"end\": 34.56, \"text\": \"This is a map of the 800+ rallies taking place across America.\"}, {\"start\": 34.56, \"end\": 44.68, \"text\": \"The event was organized by survivors of the school shooting that left 17 people dead in\"}, {\"start\": 44.68, \"end\": 46.64, \"text\": \"Parkland, Florida last month.\"}, {\"start\": 46.64, \"end\": 53.6, \"text\": \"The demonstrators say they were tired of hearing politicians say \\\"Our thoughts and prayers are with you.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 53.6, \"end\": 63.0, \"text\": \"They are demanding action, calling for stricter gun control laws and safer schools.\"}, {\"start\": 63.0, \"end\": 70.3, \"text\": \"Celebrities became advocates, teachers became activists and parents became protesters.\"}, {\"start\": 72.98, \"end\": 79.22, \"text\": \"Among the youngest people to address the crowd at Washington's \\\"March For Our Lives\\\" rally\"}, {\"start\": 79.22, \"end\": 85.56, \"text\": \"Saturday was nine-year-old Yolanda Renee King.\"}, {\"start\": 85.58, \"end\": 103.08, \"text\": \"She is the oldest granddaughter of civil rights icon and Nobel Prize winner Martin Luther King Jr.\"}, {\"start\": 103.08, \"end\": 108.06, \"text\": \"She began her remarks by telling the crowd about a famous dream her grandfather had,\"}, {\"start\": 108.06, \"end\": 112.38, \"text\": \"that \\\"his four little children would not be judged by the color of their skin but by the\"}, {\"start\": 112.38, \"end\": 115.26, \"text\": \"content of their character.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 115.48, \"end\": 120.68, \"text\": \"Then she said I have a dream: \\\"That enough is enough.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 120.68, \"end\": 126.2, \"text\": \"She also said the world needs to be one that is gun-free.\"}, {\"start\": 126.2, \"end\": 132.42, \"text\": \"After her remarks, she told CNN that she was quite nervous when she got on stage.\"}, {\"start\": 132.48, \"end\": 135.68, \"text\": \"But once she got used to the crowd, it wasn't that bad.\"}, {\"start\": 137.82, \"end\": 144.84, \"text\": \"The calendar may say it's spring but winter is still refusing to leave much of the Northeast,\"}, {\"start\": 144.84, \"end\": 151.14, \"text\": \"including in Pennsylvania where residents are not happy about it.\"}, {\"start\": 151.2, \"end\": 165.74, \"text\": \"They are so unhappy that one Sheriff's office has put America's most famous groundhog on\"}, {\"start\": 165.74, \"end\": 168.3, \"text\": \"his most wanted list.\"}, {\"start\": 168.3, \"end\": 172.46, \"text\": \"Punxsutawney Phil is now wanted fugitive.\"}, {\"start\": 172.46, \"end\": 174.38, \"text\": \"The charge?\"}, {\"start\": 174.38, \"end\": 178.52, \"text\": \"Deception!\"}, {\"start\": 178.62, \"end\": 184.16, \"text\": \"Phil was last seen promising just six more weeks of winter.\"}, {\"start\": 184.16, \"end\": 189.8, \"text\": \"That promise has now expired and freezing Pennsylvanians are crying \\\"fake news\\\" and\"}, {\"start\": 189.88, \"end\": 192.94, \"text\": \"demanding justice!\"}, {\"start\": 196.06, \"end\": 206.24, \"text\": \"Apple wants emojis that represent people with disabilities better.\"}, {\"start\": 206.28, \"end\": 212.08, \"text\": \"The company sent a proposal to Unicode, the organization that sets the global standard\"}, {\"start\": 212.08, \"end\": 220.28, \"text\": \"for emojis, and asked for 13 new additions.\"}, {\"start\": 220.28, \"end\": 230.32, \"text\": \"They include an ear with a hearing aid, a person in a wheelchair, a prosthetic arm,\"}, {\"start\": 230.34, \"end\": 235.68, \"text\": \"a service dog and a person with a cane.\"}, {\"start\": 235.68, \"end\": 240.26, \"text\": \"Apple said it shows options that are most inclusive to people in four main categories:\"}, {\"start\": 240.26, \"end\": 250.84, \"text\": \"blind and low vision, deaf and hard of hearing, physical motor disabilities and hidden disabilities.\"}, {\"start\": 250.84, \"end\": 256.46, \"text\": \"Apple says this is just a starting point not a comprehensive list of all disability emojis.\"}, {\"start\": 256.46, \"end\": 264.5, \"text\": \"If Unicode adopts the emojis, it will release guidelines so that software designers can\"}, {\"start\": 264.5, \"end\": 266.32, \"text\": \"make versions for their platforms.\"}, {\"start\": 266.32, \"end\": 272.54, \"text\": \"We would love to hear your thoughts on adding disability emojis.\"}, {\"start\": 272.54, \"end\": 282.9, \"text\": \"Send us your comments on our Facebook page, either typed or a video, and we will share\"}, {\"start\": 282.9, \"end\": 284.68, \"text\": \"some of them in tomorrow's show.\"}, {\"start\": 287.3, \"end\": 301.54, \"text\": \"Award-winning deaf rapper Sean Forbes performed in Atlanta earlier this week at Atlanta Area\"}, {\"start\": 301.54, \"end\": 303.58, \"text\": \"School for the Deaf.\"}, {\"start\": 303.58, \"end\": 305.48, \"text\": \"The place was packed!\"}, {\"start\": 305.48, \"end\": 308.94, \"text\": \"Forbes has a huge fan base.\"}, {\"start\": 309.06, \"end\": 320.08, \"text\": \"His message of living \\\"deaf and loud\\\" has impacted and empowered many people.\"}, {\"start\": 320.08, \"end\": 328.1, \"text\": \"Sign1News anchor Jethro Wooddall got an opportunity to sit and chat with Forbes before the show\"}, {\"start\": 328.1, \"end\": 331.3, \"text\": \"to hear his story.\"}, {\"start\": 331.3, \"end\": 333.56, \"text\": \"Enjoy the interview.\"}, {\"start\": 335.16, \"end\": 337.84, \"text\": \"So why are you here performing in Atlanta?\"}, {\"start\": 337.84, \"end\": 343.28, \"text\": \"The school decided to bring me here for two reasons: first to interact with the kids this\"}, {\"start\": 343.28, \"end\": 350.82, \"text\": \"morning and to share my story and life's journey and then to perform for the deaf community.\"}, {\"start\": 350.82, \"end\": 354.74, \"text\": \"The interesting thing is I was right here in this exact room 10 years ago interviewing\"}, {\"start\": 354.76, \"end\": 358.74, \"text\": \"with CNN.\"}, {\"start\": 358.74, \"end\": 361.58, \"text\": \"So this is really taking me back.\"}, {\"start\": 361.58, \"end\": 363.08, \"text\": \"That's awesome.\"}, {\"start\": 363.08, \"end\": 365.0, \"text\": \"So you're telling me 10 years ago...\"}, {\"start\": 365.0, \"end\": 370.36, \"text\": \"Yes 10 years ago I performed here, similar situation.\"}, {\"start\": 370.36, \"end\": 374.66, \"text\": \"So now 10 years later I feel I have come full circle.\"}, {\"start\": 374.66, \"end\": 375.92, \"text\": \"You blink and you're back.\"}, {\"start\": 378.2, \"end\": 384.36, \"text\": \"So how did you develop this dream of becoming a rapper?\"}, {\"start\": 384.38, \"end\": 386.76, \"text\": \"Really it just happened.\"}, {\"start\": 386.84, \"end\": 389.3, \"text\": \"Growing up I was always fascinated with music.\"}, {\"start\": 389.3, \"end\": 395.06, \"text\": \"I always wanted to write songs, play drums, just have fun with music.\"}, {\"start\": 395.06, \"end\": 399.4, \"text\": \"I really didn't start rapping until I was about 12 or 13 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 399.4, \"end\": 400.52, \"text\": \"I was blown away by it.\"}, {\"start\": 400.52, \"end\": 410.92, \"text\": \"When I was growing up my parents and two brothers loved rock, acid rock and heavy metal.\"}, {\"start\": 410.92, \"end\": 413.3, \"text\": \"It was really different when I was growing up.\"}, {\"start\": 413.3, \"end\": 420.5, \"text\": \"But when I discovered rap music, it truly spoke to me for a number of reasons.\"}, {\"start\": 420.5, \"end\": 429.92, \"text\": \"One, rap has a rhythm and since I'm a drummer (I've been drumming since I was five)... so\"}, {\"start\": 429.92, \"end\": 434.82, \"text\": \"with the rhythm and drums, I feel like rap just really resonated me.\"}, {\"start\": 435.0, \"end\": 439.22, \"text\": \"So you are truly feeling the rhythm?\"}, {\"start\": 439.22, \"end\": 444.64, \"text\": \"So your parents love classic rock but your sister...\"}, {\"start\": 444.64, \"end\": 447.36, \"text\": \"No I have two brothers.\"}, {\"start\": 447.36, \"end\": 449.72, \"text\": \"Okay I'm not gonna question their preference of music.\"}, {\"start\": 449.72, \"end\": 451.7, \"text\": \"I think I'm going to stick to the rap.\"}, {\"start\": 451.7, \"end\": 452.9, \"text\": \"I love heavy metal.\"}, {\"start\": 454.4, \"end\": 458.82, \"text\": \"I like all music and respect all genres.\"}, {\"start\": 458.88, \"end\": 463.58, \"text\": \"People always ask me what do I have a preference for and honestly I like art.\"}, {\"start\": 463.58, \"end\": 466.62, \"text\": \"I listen, experience and feel.\"}, {\"start\": 466.66, \"end\": 468.78, \"text\": \"Music about feeling.\"}, {\"start\": 468.78, \"end\": 471.66, \"text\": \"Sometimes people take it too literally.\"}, {\"start\": 471.8, \"end\": 473.54, \"text\": \"Like \\\"feeling.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 473.58, \"end\": 478.78, \"text\": \"I'm talking about connecting with what the artist is saying.\"}, {\"start\": 478.78, \"end\": 483.88, \"text\": \"When I started signing music, I started with other artists' songs so people could understand\"}, {\"start\": 483.88, \"end\": 486.78, \"text\": \"what the artist was saying.\"}, {\"start\": 486.78, \"end\": 497.2, \"text\": \"Like right now, before this performance, that Matt Maxey, he is really expressing the culture.\"}, {\"start\": 497.2, \"end\": 499.0, \"text\": \"I love that music.\"}, {\"start\": 499.04, \"end\": 505.7, \"text\": \"So for me, I see what he is doing and what I was doing 10 years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 505.7, \"end\": 512.7, \"text\": \"I feel he's really expressing the artist within.\"}, {\"start\": 512.7, \"end\": 518.76, \"text\": \"Matt has that swag, that personality so I applaud him.\"}, {\"start\": 518.76, \"end\": 519.88, \"text\": \"I'm a big fan.\"}, {\"start\": 521.9, \"end\": 524.92, \"text\": \"So let's talk about you loving all artists and genres of music.\"}, {\"start\": 524.92, \"end\": 525.44, \"text\": \"I'm curious.\"}, {\"start\": 525.44, \"end\": 526.82, \"text\": \"What about country music?\"}, {\"start\": 526.82, \"end\": 528.28, \"text\": \"I love country music!\"}, {\"start\": 528.28, \"end\": 529.56, \"text\": \"Oh yes.\"}, {\"start\": 529.56, \"end\": 530.9, \"text\": \"I love country music.\"}, {\"start\": 530.9, \"end\": 534.48, \"text\": \"My father worked for a country music group.\"}, {\"start\": 534.54, \"end\": 543.44, \"text\": \"So I grew up with country music, the Eagles, all those guys.\"}, {\"start\": 544.16, \"end\": 547.96, \"text\": \"Okay so what do you mean you been rapping for 10 years now?\"}, {\"start\": 550.18, \"end\": 552.18, \"text\": \"Okay well... let me go back.\"}, {\"start\": 552.18, \"end\": 554.82, \"text\": \"I discovered rap when I was about 12 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 554.82, \"end\": 561.54, \"text\": \"I didn't start signing until I was 10 or 11 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 561.54, \"end\": 566.0, \"text\": \"I really didn't start signing rap until I was in college at RIT.\"}, {\"start\": 566.0, \"end\": 576.74, \"text\": \"It was really kind of awkward but my skills have evolved over the past 10 years.\"}, {\"start\": 577.58, \"end\": 580.6, \"text\": \"I feel like when I was watching a video of myself it's like...\"}, {\"start\": 580.82, \"end\": 582.04, \"text\": \"Now you know how I feel!\"}, {\"start\": 582.04, \"end\": 584.0, \"text\": \"I feel that way all the time with my signing.\"}, {\"start\": 584.0, \"end\": 590.52, \"text\": \"When I recorded myself signing here at Atlanta Area School for the Deaf and...so I know how\"}, {\"start\": 590.52, \"end\": 592.42, \"text\": \"you feel.\"}, {\"start\": 592.94, \"end\": 596.32, \"text\": \"So you been in the rap game for about 10 years.\"}, {\"start\": 596.32, \"end\": 597.86, \"text\": \"How many albums do you have?\"}, {\"start\": 597.86, \"end\": 600.0, \"text\": \"I've only put out one album.\"}, {\"start\": 600.0, \"end\": 601.12, \"text\": \"Just one.\"}, {\"start\": 601.12, \"end\": 602.48, \"text\": \"I thought there were several albums.\"}, {\"start\": 602.48, \"end\": 603.6, \"text\": \"No just the one.\"}, {\"start\": 603.6, \"end\": 607.26, \"text\": \"I put out several different songs but only one album.\"}, {\"start\": 607.28, \"end\": 609.3, \"text\": \"But I have a little bit of news to share.\"}, {\"start\": 609.46, \"end\": 611.24, \"text\": \"I just finished a new album.\"}, {\"start\": 611.46, \"end\": 613.12, \"text\": \"I just finished two weeks ago.\"}, {\"start\": 613.12, \"end\": 615.82, \"text\": \"It is ready to be released soon.\"}, {\"start\": 615.82, \"end\": 617.64, \"text\": \"That is exciting news!\"}, {\"start\": 617.64, \"end\": 623.3, \"text\": \"I've finished making the music, writing songs and now I'm working on the music video because\"}, {\"start\": 623.3, \"end\": 626.48, \"text\": \"I believe music should be accessible for everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 626.48, \"end\": 628.5, \"text\": \"I want hearing people to enjoy it.\"}, {\"start\": 628.5, \"end\": 632.44, \"text\": \"The goal of this album is more visual.\"}, {\"start\": 632.6, \"end\": 639.36, \"text\": \"When hearing people listen to music they can visualize and imagine.\"}, {\"start\": 639.36, \"end\": 646.98, \"text\": \"For me, my last album, it was visual also but visual in a way that you could see what\"}, {\"start\": 646.98, \"end\": 648.56, \"text\": \"the song means.\"}, {\"start\": 649.06, \"end\": 653.1, \"text\": \"The way I make music videos you can see what I'm saying this time.\"}, {\"start\": 653.76, \"end\": 662.1, \"text\": \"I wanted to show the music, show my ASL, show my expression, to show what it looks like.\"}, {\"start\": 663.64, \"end\": 666.76, \"text\": \"I know it's a little bit far out.\"}, {\"start\": 667.34, \"end\": 669.2, \"text\": \"I'm so looking forward to that.\"}, {\"start\": 669.34, \"end\": 671.26, \"text\": \"Can't wait to see it.\"}, {\"start\": 671.56, \"end\": 672.98, \"text\": \"That's exciting.\"}, {\"start\": 672.98, \"end\": 676.94, \"text\": \"Do you write and sign your own songs?\"}, {\"start\": 676.94, \"end\": 685.58, \"text\": \"I write my own lyrics but also work with a producer named Jake Bass who writes music.\"}, {\"start\": 685.58, \"end\": 692.54, \"text\": \"For this album and the last one I was involved with every song from the start.\"}, {\"start\": 692.56, \"end\": 701.74, \"text\": \"For example, for a new song I would play the drums and then write.\"}, {\"start\": 701.74, \"end\": 707.58, \"text\": \"It was an interesting process for me because on the last album Jake gave me all the music\"}, {\"start\": 707.58, \"end\": 711.38, \"text\": \"and I got to pick which ones I liked.\"}, {\"start\": 711.38, \"end\": 713.36, \"text\": \"Really I like everything he makes.\"}, {\"start\": 713.68, \"end\": 722.76, \"text\": \"He's made over 100 different songs so you become very selective with the song you put out.\"}, {\"start\": 725.48, \"end\": 738.18, \"text\": \"So now that you are in Atlanta what message do you have for children who have big dreams?\"}, {\"start\": 738.18, \"end\": 742.04, \"text\": \"Well the journey is not always what you expect.\"}, {\"start\": 742.04, \"end\": 744.9, \"text\": \"You have to expect the unexpected.\"}, {\"start\": 744.9, \"end\": 749.55, \"text\": \"For example my journey, I really wanted to arrive on the music scene but my journey is\"}, {\"start\": 749.55, \"end\": 751.38, \"text\": \"taking me everywhere, to different places.\"}, {\"start\": 751.38, \"end\": 758.16, \"text\": \"I established DPAN-TV to make music accessible and that is a challenge.\"}, {\"start\": 758.16, \"end\": 763.48, \"text\": \"The music business doesn't really understand where the deaf community is coming from.\"}, {\"start\": 763.48, \"end\": 767.96, \"text\": \"It would be nice to see Matt continue his journey with DPAN-TV.\"}, {\"start\": 767.96, \"end\": 772.06, \"text\": \"I really want to make a platform for signing content.\"}, {\"start\": 772.06, \"end\": 779.62, \"text\": \"That's really my goal with DPAN-TV because I feel like, for DPan, all of our music is\"}, {\"start\": 779.62, \"end\": 783.06, \"text\": \"released through YouTube.\"}, {\"start\": 783.06, \"end\": 789.3, \"text\": \"And that's a little sad because we spend so much time and energy on those videos, a lot\"}, {\"start\": 789.3, \"end\": 797.62, \"text\": \"of money, and when you search for your favorite video, YouTube has a zillion videos show up.\"}, {\"start\": 797.82, \"end\": 801.1, \"text\": \"You don't know what's good and what's bad.\"}, {\"start\": 801.1, \"end\": 808.88, \"text\": \"So sometimes I feel is not beneficial for those who want to learn a language.\"}, {\"start\": 808.88, \"end\": 815.08, \"text\": \"It's like \\\"Oh I saw this cool video\\\" but the signing is awful.\"}, {\"start\": 815.08, \"end\": 820.32, \"text\": \"I'm in favor of people learning our language.\"}, {\"start\": 820.32, \"end\": 821.42, \"text\": \"Of course.\"}, {\"start\": 822.48, \"end\": 827.2, \"text\": \"But at the same time there needs to be a level of respect as well.\"}, {\"start\": 828.32, \"end\": 835.8, \"text\": \"It's just with DPAN-TV everything were doing is about trying to be original.\"}, {\"start\": 836.5, \"end\": 845.1, \"text\": \"So bottom line, your message is to expect the unexpected and be original.\"}, {\"start\": 845.1, \"end\": 846.52, \"text\": \"Be original! Yes!\"}, {\"start\": 846.52, \"end\": 848.5, \"text\": \"I like that.\"}, {\"start\": 848.5, \"end\": 850.2, \"text\": \"Thank you for taking the time to sit and chat.\"}, {\"start\": 850.2, \"end\": 852.14, \"text\": \"I know you have to go and get ready to perform.\"}, {\"start\": 852.14, \"end\": 853.78, \"text\": \"I hope you enjoy the show tonight.\"}, {\"start\": 853.78, \"end\": 854.78, \"text\": \"Oh you know I will.\"}, {\"start\": 854.78, \"end\": 856.0, \"text\": \"If he stays.\"}, {\"start\": 856.0, \"end\": 862.04, \"text\": \"Maybe he so busy he's got to jet off to interview another person, I don't know.\"}, {\"start\": 862.16, \"end\": 864.88, \"text\": \"Okay truth be told, I'm your number one fan.\"}, {\"start\": 864.88, \"end\": 866.68, \"text\": \"Don't tell them.\"}, {\"start\": 866.68, \"end\": 868.82, \"text\": \"You will see him on the front row rockin' out.\"}, {\"start\": 868.82, \"end\": 872.22, \"text\": \"It's more like this, not this.\"}, {\"start\": 872.24, \"end\": 875.84, \"text\": \"I like this.\"}, {\"start\": 875.84, \"end\": 877.6, \"text\": \"I'll remember that next time.\"}, {\"start\": 877.6, \"end\": 880.32, \"text\": \"Thank you.\"}, {\"start\": 881.14, \"end\": 884.64, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching my interview with Sean Forbes.\"}, {\"start\": 884.76, \"end\": 888.08, \"text\": \"Back to you in the Sign1News studio.\"}, {\"start\": 888.14, \"end\": 889.82, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 894.1, \"end\": 896.34, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 896.34, \"end\": 898.1, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 898.1, \"end\": 900.68, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 900.68, \"end\": 906.14, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 906.22, \"end\": 914.44, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "6Pdev_juHdM": {
    "video_id": "6Pdev_juHdM",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.19.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171220",
    "duration": 465,
    "view_count": 386,
    "description": "December 19, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-AMTRAK TRAIN DERAILMENT CLEAN UP BEGINS\n-FORMER \"GLEE\" STAR PLEADS GUILTY IN CHILD PORN CASE\n-DO YOU BELIEVE IN UFOS?\n-PRINCE HARRY APPOINTED TO NEW JOB\n-FACEBOOK TO ALERT USERS SPOTTED IN UNTAGGED PICS\n-SAY \"NO\" TO RAW DOUGH\n-PANDA CUB MAKES ITS DEBUT\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE Our talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.56, \"end\": 6.72, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.72, \"end\": 8.9, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.9, \"end\": 10.58, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 10.62, \"end\": 13.48, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.48, \"end\": 22.18, \"text\": \"The cleanup has begun following Monday's deadly train derailment in Washington State.\"}, {\"start\": 22.18, \"end\": 29.62, \"text\": \"The National Transportation Safety Board (NTSB) and state officials are working around the\"}, {\"start\": 29.62, \"end\": 36.6, \"text\": \"clock to clear the wreckage\"}, {\"start\": 36.6, \"end\": 40.28, \"text\": \"and they have blocked interstate that runs below the tracks.\"}, {\"start\": 40.28, \"end\": 44.06, \"text\": \"Although the NTSB says the cause of the cause of the derailment has yet not been determined,\"}, {\"start\": 44.06, \"end\": 48.56, \"text\": \"it has said the train was traveling at nearly 3 times the speed limit --\"}, {\"start\": 48.6, \"end\": 54.56, \"text\": \"80 mph in a 30 mph zone.\"}, {\"start\": 54.56, \"end\": 59.2, \"text\": \"Three people were killed and more than 100 were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 59.2, \"end\": 65.96, \"text\": \"Passengers inside the train say it sounded like an exploding bomb when the train crashed.\"}, {\"start\": 69.44, \"end\": 83.04, \"text\": \"Former \\\"Glee\\\" actor Mark Salling has pleaded guilty to possessing child porn involving\"}, {\"start\": 83.04, \"end\": 87.12, \"text\": \"a pre-pubescent minor.\"}, {\"start\": 87.12, \"end\": 90.96, \"text\": \"Salling made his plea Monday at a Los Angeles courthouse, two months after he reportedly\"}, {\"start\": 90.96, \"end\": 97.8, \"text\": \"struck a deal with authorities.\"}, {\"start\": 97.88, \"end\": 108.4, \"text\": \"Federal investigators say they found more than 25,000 child porn images and 600 videos\"}, {\"start\": 108.4, \"end\": 114.92, \"text\": \"on Salling's computers and thumb drives.\"}, {\"start\": 114.92, \"end\": 121.92, \"text\": \"\\\"People\\\" magazine reports that some of the content depicted children as young as\"}, {\"start\": 121.92, \"end\": 127.64, \"text\": \"3-years old being abused.\"}, {\"start\": 127.64, \"end\": 136.4, \"text\": \"Salling has reportedly agreed to be sentenced to 4 to 7 years in prison and will be under\"}, {\"start\": 136.4, \"end\": 140.08, \"text\": \"supervised release for another 20 years.\"}, {\"start\": 140.08, \"end\": 146.92, \"text\": \"He will also have to register as a sex offender.\"}, {\"start\": 146.92, \"end\": 151.88, \"text\": \"In a statement, Salling's attorney says his client wants to accept responsibility for\"}, {\"start\": 151.88, \"end\": 153.72, \"text\": \"his conduct.\"}, {\"start\": 153.72, \"end\": 159.08, \"text\": \"He will be sentenced in March.\"}, {\"start\": 162.24, \"end\": 167.32, \"text\": \"Do you believe in unidentified flying objects (UFOs)?\"}, {\"start\": 167.32, \"end\": 177.88, \"text\": \"The U-S Department of Defense has released video from a Navy jet pilot spotting an unidentified\"}, {\"start\": 177.88, \"end\": 181.56, \"text\": \"flying object over San Diego in 2004.\"}, {\"start\": 181.56, \"end\": 182.36, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 193.96, \"end\": 197.32, \"text\": \"The video was released as part of a program only recently acknowledged\"}, {\"start\": 197.32, \"end\": 200.08, \"text\": \"by the Defense Department.\"}, {\"start\": 200.08, \"end\": 206.88, \"text\": \"It was called the \\\"Advanced Aerospace Threat Identification\\\" program and it looked into\"}, {\"start\": 206.96, \"end\": 215.08, \"text\": \"reports of unidentified flying objects.\"}, {\"start\": 215.08, \"end\": 222.76, \"text\": \"But according to the New York Times, funding for the program ended in 2012.\"}, {\"start\": 227.6, \"end\": 234.76, \"text\": \"Prince Harry has been assigned to a new role.\"}, {\"start\": 234.76, \"end\": 242.96, \"text\": \"The Royal family tweeted on Tuesday that the Queen confirmed Prince Harry as the new Captain\"}, {\"start\": 242.96, \"end\": 245.2, \"text\": \"General Royal Marines.\"}, {\"start\": 245.2, \"end\": 252.8, \"text\": \"He will take over for his grandfather, the Duke of Edinburgh,\"}, {\"start\": 252.8, \"end\": 255.02, \"text\": \"who has held the role since 1953.\"}, {\"start\": 255.02, \"end\": 260.16, \"text\": \"Prince Harry served in the Army for 10 years, rising to the rank of captain\"}, {\"start\": 260.16, \"end\": 266.44, \"text\": \"and undertaking two tours of Afghanistan.\"}, {\"start\": 268.2, \"end\": 278.92, \"text\": \"Facebook is now using facial recognition technology to alert users when a photo of them is uploaded,\"}, {\"start\": 278.92, \"end\": 282.16, \"text\": \"even if the user isn't tagged in it.\"}, {\"start\": 282.16, \"end\": 291.56, \"text\": \"Members can message anyone who posts a photo of them and ask that it be taken down.\"}, {\"start\": 291.56, \"end\": 298.52, \"text\": \"Users can also formally request that Facebook remove a photo.\"}, {\"start\": 298.52, \"end\": 306.8, \"text\": \"While the new tool does raise some privacy concerns, Facebook says it will not use facial\"}, {\"start\": 306.8, \"end\": 310.48, \"text\": \"recognition to better target advertisements.\"}, {\"start\": 312.28, \"end\": 321.44, \"text\": \"This time of year homes are full of homemade raw batters.\"}, {\"start\": 321.44, \"end\": 326.84, \"text\": \"And it can be very tempting to dig into those cookies, cakes and breads\"}, {\"start\": 326.96, \"end\": 329.2, \"text\": \"before they are cooked.\"}, {\"start\": 329.2, \"end\": 338.64, \"text\": \"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) is warning people to say \\\"no\\\" to raw\"}, {\"start\": 338.64, \"end\": 340.92, \"text\": \"dough this holiday season.\"}, {\"start\": 341.0, \"end\": 343.28, \"text\": \"It can be bad for your health.\"}, {\"start\": 343.28, \"end\": 344.44, \"text\": \"Here's why:\"}, {\"start\": 344.48, \"end\": 351.84, \"text\": \"Flour, the main ingredient for these foods, is a raw agricultural product that hasn't\"}, {\"start\": 351.84, \"end\": 355.44, \"text\": \"been treated to kill germs, such as E. coli.\"}, {\"start\": 355.44, \"end\": 364.08, \"text\": \"Any bacteria that lives within the flour is only killed off when it's cooked.\"}, {\"start\": 364.08, \"end\": 368.52, \"text\": \"Eggs are also another ingredient found in most doughs.\"}, {\"start\": 368.52, \"end\": 371.6, \"text\": \"Eggs are only safe to eat with fully cooked and handled properly.\"}, {\"start\": 371.6, \"end\": 376.68, \"text\": \"They contain salmonella.\"}, {\"start\": 376.72, \"end\": 384.24, \"text\": \"So this holiday season say \\\"no\\\" to raw dough.\"}, {\"start\": 384.24, \"end\": 390.28, \"text\": \"Back away from the batter until it is properly cooked.\"}, {\"start\": 392.24, \"end\": 407.52, \"text\": \"Adorable 6-month old panda cub Xiang Xiang and her mother Shin Shin made a special appearance\"}, {\"start\": 407.52, \"end\": 409.2, \"text\": \"before selected people, including media on Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 409.2, \"end\": 416.44, \"text\": \"This is the first time in nearly 3 decades that a cub born at the Ueno Zoo\"}, {\"start\": 416.56, \"end\": 421.52, \"text\": \"is available for the public to visit.\"}, {\"start\": 421.52, \"end\": 429.4, \"text\": \"The panda is so popular the zoo limited her public appearances to 2 1/2 hours a day and\"}, {\"start\": 429.4, \"end\": 436.4, \"text\": \"set up a lottery to select guests.\"}, {\"start\": 438.64, \"end\": 441.08, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 441.08, \"end\": 442.8, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 442.8, \"end\": 445.48, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 445.52, \"end\": 450.84, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 450.92, \"end\": 458.68, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "l_Pr8kKQInU": {
    "video_id": "l_Pr8kKQInU",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.25.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180426",
    "duration": 380,
    "view_count": 1386,
    "description": "4.25.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Police say suspected serial killer is ex-cop\n-Judge orders reopening of DACA after 90-day delay \n-Migrant caravan nears U.S. border\n-Waffle House reopens after deadly shooting\n-Meghan Markle makes final \"Suits\" appearance\n-Disney World hiring 3,500 workers for summer\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from no",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.4, \"end\": 8.66, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.66, \"end\": 11.14, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.28, \"end\": 12.98, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 12.98, \"end\": 16.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.3, \"end\": 36.12, \"text\": \"FBI officials say 72-year-old Joseph James DeAngelo has been arrested and identified\"}, {\"start\": 36.12, \"end\": 43.88, \"text\": \"as the so-called \\\"Golden State Killer.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 43.88, \"end\": 60.1, \"text\": \"Investigators believe he committed 12 killings and 48 rapes across California from 1976 to 1986.\"}, {\"start\": 60.1, \"end\": 65.42, \"text\": \"Even more shocking -- he in an ex-cop!\"}, {\"start\": 65.42, \"end\": 75.9, \"text\": \"Police say DeAngelo's rape victims were initially only women who were alone with their children\"}, {\"start\": 75.9, \"end\": 88.22, \"text\": \"but a few years later his crimes escalated to the killing of couples in their homes.\"}, {\"start\": 88.3, \"end\": 101.06, \"text\": \"Investigators say they were able to catch DeAngelo thanks to tips and eventually matching\"}, {\"start\": 101.06, \"end\": 104.88, \"text\": \"his DNA to the crime scene evidence.\"}, {\"start\": 107.38, \"end\": 115.66, \"text\": \"Another federal judge has overturned the Trump administration's plans to end the program\"}, {\"start\": 115.66, \"end\": 124.16, \"text\": \"for immigrants brought to the United States as children by their parents -- or DACA.\"}, {\"start\": 124.2, \"end\": 135.42, \"text\": \"Tuesday's ruling means new enrollees can now apply for DACA protection against deportation.\"}, {\"start\": 135.42, \"end\": 146.2, \"text\": \"Now the Trump administration has 90 days to better explain the reasons behind the ending DACA.\"}, {\"start\": 146.2, \"end\": 156.12, \"text\": \"No court has ever found DACA to be unconstitutional.\"}, {\"start\": 159.64, \"end\": 164.4, \"text\": \"More immigration news today.\"}, {\"start\": 164.4, \"end\": 178.88, \"text\": \"The caravan of Central American migrants has arrived at the city of Tijuana on the Mexico-US border.\"}, {\"start\": 178.88, \"end\": 189.6, \"text\": \"The migrants say they are fleeing rampant violence and poverty in Central America and\"}, {\"start\": 189.6, \"end\": 193.16, \"text\": \"hope they'll find safety and security in the United States.\"}, {\"start\": 193.24, \"end\": 204.24, \"text\": \"Many in the caravan say they plan to turn themselves into US authorities and ask for asylum.\"}, {\"start\": 204.24, \"end\": 212.56, \"text\": \"But President Trump has made it very clear he is not planning on rolling out the welcome mat.\"}, {\"start\": 217.34, \"end\": 229.16, \"text\": \"The Nashville-area Waffle House where a gunman killed four people over the weekend reopened\"}, {\"start\": 229.16, \"end\": 231.9, \"text\": \"on Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 231.9, \"end\": 240.02, \"text\": \"Four white crosses sit in front of the restaurant as a tribute to the victims.\"}, {\"start\": 240.02, \"end\": 246.36, \"text\": \"Waffle House officials say they are planning on erecting a permanent memorial in their honor.\"}, {\"start\": 246.36, \"end\": 253.44, \"text\": \"The restaurant has also pledged to donate all the proceeds for the next month to the\"}, {\"start\": 253.44, \"end\": 256.72, \"text\": \"families of both the living and deceased victims.\"}, {\"start\": 258.56, \"end\": 271.14, \"text\": \"Actress and future princess Meghan Markle said farewell to her acting career tonight.\"}, {\"start\": 271.14, \"end\": 279.32, \"text\": \"Tonight she made her last appearance on USA network's \\\"Suits.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 279.32, \"end\": 287.3, \"text\": \"She played the character Rachel Zane for seven seasons.\"}, {\"start\": 287.32, \"end\": 296.6, \"text\": \"Markle is set to marry Prince Harry in London on May 19 and she said she planned to quit\"}, {\"start\": 296.6, \"end\": 298.74, \"text\": \"acting after her marriage.\"}, {\"start\": 301.88, \"end\": 308.42, \"text\": \"The happiest place on earth is hiring.\"}, {\"start\": 308.42, \"end\": 317.9, \"text\": \"Disney World in Orlando, Florida is looking to fill 3,500 positions in time for the busy\"}, {\"start\": 317.9, \"end\": 319.86, \"text\": \"summer season.\"}, {\"start\": 319.9, \"end\": 330.16, \"text\": \"Full-time, part-time and seasonal jobs are available in housekeeping, transportation,\"}, {\"start\": 330.16, \"end\": 334.3, \"text\": \"lifeguarding and food and beverage teams.\"}, {\"start\": 334.3, \"end\": 347.34, \"text\": \"If you are interested in applying, go to parksjob.disneycareers.com.\"}, {\"start\": 351.34, \"end\": 354.08, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 354.08, \"end\": 355.22, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 355.22, \"end\": 358.54, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 358.54, \"end\": 364.86, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 364.92, \"end\": 367.32, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 367.32, \"end\": 369.02, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 369.02, \"end\": 371.82, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-cyCLrQnXZo": {
    "video_id": "-cyCLrQnXZo",
    "title": "Sign1News 5.31.19 - News for the Deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20190601",
    "duration": 611,
    "view_count": 1396,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Atlantic hurricane season starts June 1\n-Slow moving disaster unfolding in Arkansas\n-Historic 8-way tie in National Scripps Spelling Bee\n-Police release Smollett documents\n-R. Kelly charged with 11 new counts\n-11-ft gator breaks into home!\n-‘Avozilla’ avocados hit stores",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 29.62, \"end\": 31.78, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 31.78, \"end\": 33.42, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 33.42, \"end\": 34.58, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 34.58, \"end\": 37.84, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 41.3, \"end\": 47.3, \"text\": \"Hurricane season starts this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 47.3, \"end\": 61.06, \"text\": \"Government forecasters are predicting a near-normal Atlantic hurricane season this year.\"}, {\"start\": 61.06, \"end\": 72.74, \"text\": \"That means 9 to 15 named storms are likely with 2 to 4 Category 3 hurricanes with winds\"}, {\"start\": 72.74, \"end\": 75.82, \"text\": \"exceeding 110 mph.\"}, {\"start\": 75.82, \"end\": 84.6, \"text\": \"But the Atlantic Ocean is expected to see warmer than average temperatures, so when\"}, {\"start\": 84.6, \"end\": 90.82, \"text\": \"storms do form they could be powerful.\"}, {\"start\": 90.82, \"end\": 98.4, \"text\": \"However some researchers point out that the most important aspects of hurricanes can't\"}, {\"start\": 98.4, \"end\": 104.92, \"text\": \"be predicted: how many will make landfall.\"}, {\"start\": 104.92, \"end\": 113.8, \"text\": \"This year has already seen one named storm: subtropical storm Andrea.\"}, {\"start\": 113.8, \"end\": 121.4, \"text\": \"It set a record for marking the fifth consecutive year an unnamed storm has formed before the\"}, {\"start\": 121.4, \"end\": 125.92, \"text\": \"official start of hurricane season.\"}, {\"start\": 132.56, \"end\": 138.9, \"text\": \"Right now there is an emergency in Arkansas.\"}, {\"start\": 138.9, \"end\": 149.62, \"text\": \"After already facing tornadoes and deadly floods this week, the state is preparing for\"}, {\"start\": 149.62, \"end\": 155.14, \"text\": \"historic flooding that's expected to wreck havoc across the state for weeks to come.\"}, {\"start\": 155.14, \"end\": 163.48, \"text\": \"Rising waters from the Arkansas River have taken over entire communities.\"}, {\"start\": 163.48, \"end\": 171.84, \"text\": \"The National Weather Service said that every large community along the Arkansas River is\"}, {\"start\": 171.84, \"end\": 176.32, \"text\": \"going to be affected, with major flooding over the next seven days.\"}, {\"start\": 176.32, \"end\": 195.48, \"text\": \"The Dardanelle levee, some 70 miles upstream from Little Rock, breached overnight, leaving\"}, {\"start\": 195.5, \"end\": 202.42, \"text\": \"what one official called a \\\"wide open hole of water.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 202.42, \"end\": 212.34, \"text\": \"Ports are now shut down along the swollen river, delivering a devastating blow to the\"}, {\"start\": 212.34, \"end\": 214.74, \"text\": \"state's economy.\"}, {\"start\": 214.74, \"end\": 223.7, \"text\": \"Officials say the state is set to lose $23 million a day.\"}, {\"start\": 223.7, \"end\": 239.92, \"text\": \"Also a levee failure on the Mississippi River has caused mandatory evacuations for residents\"}, {\"start\": 239.92, \"end\": 242.32, \"text\": \"in West Quincy, Missouri.\"}, {\"start\": 242.32, \"end\": 250.64, \"text\": \"More than 300 roads are underwater with the potential for more to come.\"}, {\"start\": 257.8, \"end\": 269.28, \"text\": \"History was made Thursday night at the 92nd Scripps national spelling bee.\"}, {\"start\": 269.28, \"end\": 278.68, \"text\": \"After 20 rounds, the bee ended with eight co-champions.\"}, {\"start\": 278.68, \"end\": 281.34, \"text\": \"That's right...8!\"}, {\"start\": 281.34, \"end\": 290.54, \"text\": \"After the 17th round, organizers realized that there were only enough challenging words\"}, {\"start\": 290.54, \"end\": 293.5, \"text\": \"left for three final rounds.\"}, {\"start\": 293.5, \"end\": 302.1, \"text\": \"Sure enough, all of the remaining competitors spelled those words perfectly.\"}, {\"start\": 302.1, \"end\": 308.06, \"text\": \"All eight will receive a $50,000 prize.\"}, {\"start\": 308.06, \"end\": 317.26, \"text\": \"This year's national spelling bee featured 562 contestants ages 15 and younger, representing\"}, {\"start\": 317.26, \"end\": 323.48, \"text\": \"all 50 US states as well as several territories and countries.\"}, {\"start\": 328.1, \"end\": 338.54, \"text\": \"On Thursday, Chicago police released 460 pages from the Jussie Smollett investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 338.54, \"end\": 347.38, \"text\": \"The documents includes arrest reports, case reports and supplementary files.\"}, {\"start\": 347.38, \"end\": 356.68, \"text\": \"They also reveal that Chicago detectives knew about a possible deal in the case a month\"}, {\"start\": 356.68, \"end\": 361.08, \"text\": \"before charges were actually dropped.\"}, {\"start\": 361.08, \"end\": 375.84, \"text\": \"The records were unsealed last week despite objections from Smollett's legal team.\"}, {\"start\": 375.84, \"end\": 383.94, \"text\": \"Smollett originally faced 16 felony charges in connection with his claim that he was the\"}, {\"start\": 383.94, \"end\": 393.98, \"text\": \"victim of a crime in January, which authorities came to believe was false.\"}, {\"start\": 393.98, \"end\": 405.18, \"text\": \"Investigators said he made up the story and paid two brothers of Nigerian descent to stage\"}, {\"start\": 405.18, \"end\": 407.72, \"text\": \"the attack.\"}, {\"start\": 407.72, \"end\": 416.56, \"text\": \"The charges against the actor and former star of Empire were dropped on March 26.\"}, {\"start\": 420.48, \"end\": 429.84, \"text\": \"The legal troubles are mounting for R and B singer R Kelly.\"}, {\"start\": 429.84, \"end\": 440.72, \"text\": \"Kelly is facing 11 new counts of sexual assault and sexual abuse charges.\"}, {\"start\": 440.74, \"end\": 449.92, \"text\": \"The Cook County states Attorney's office filed the charges Thursday in Illinois.\"}, {\"start\": 449.92, \"end\": 458.06, \"text\": \"According to the document, at least three of the charges relate to a victim between\"}, {\"start\": 458.06, \"end\": 461.74, \"text\": \"the ages of 13 and 16.\"}, {\"start\": 461.74, \"end\": 472.56, \"text\": \"The new counts bring the total number of charges against Kelly to 21 in Illinois.\"}, {\"start\": 475.06, \"end\": 483.44, \"text\": \"Here's something you don't want to see inside your home ever!\"}, {\"start\": 487.6, \"end\": 498.63, \"text\": \"An 11-foot long alligator made its way into the kitchen of a Clearwater, Florida home overnight.\"}, {\"start\": 498.64, \"end\": 509.6, \"text\": \"It smashed a low-level window and, for whatever reason, went straight for the wine.\"}, {\"start\": 509.6, \"end\": 514.56, \"text\": \"The homeowner says it broke several bottles.\"}, {\"start\": 514.56, \"end\": 518.6, \"text\": \"No one was hurt and the gator was removed safely.\"}, {\"start\": 522.72, \"end\": 529.84, \"text\": \"Check out the size of this avocado!\"}, {\"start\": 533.4, \"end\": 545.04, \"text\": \"It's nicknamed \\\"avoizilla\\\" because it's five times the size of a normal avocado.\"}, {\"start\": 545.04, \"end\": 554.36, \"text\": \"This green giant is grown by a farmer in central Queensland.\"}, {\"start\": 554.37, \"end\": 563.25, \"text\": \"It weighs in at almost 3 pounds and can cost up to $16 for a single berry.\"}, {\"start\": 563.25, \"end\": 570.8, \"text\": \"It's not the first time it's been available in stores but it's still catching shoppers off guard.\"}, {\"start\": 574.7, \"end\": 578.08, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 578.08, \"end\": 580.12, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 580.12, \"end\": 583.42, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 583.42, \"end\": 595.56, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us in all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our app also.\"}, {\"start\": 595.56, \"end\": 597.24, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 597.24, \"end\": 598.76, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 598.76, \"end\": 602.12, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "MC3PN3Sl218": {
    "video_id": "MC3PN3Sl218",
    "title": "Snow fall in the desert! (ASL 1.30.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180131",
    "duration": 32,
    "view_count": 111,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.7, \"end\": 5.06, \"text\": \"Take a look at this.\"}, {\"start\": 5.06, \"end\": 7.98, \"text\": \"That is snow in the desert!\"}, {\"start\": 7.98, \"end\": 14.04, \"text\": \"For the past two days several regions of Morocco have experienced snowfall.\"}, {\"start\": 14.04, \"end\": 18.54, \"text\": \"It's not unusual to see snow in the northern mountainous parts of Morocco, but this snow\"}, {\"start\": 18.54, \"end\": 21.94, \"text\": \"fell in the southern region, a very rare occurrence.\"}, {\"start\": 21.94, \"end\": 28.58, \"text\": \"Residents say this is the first time they've witnessed snowfall in the desert in more than\"}, {\"start\": 28.58, \"end\": 30.4, \"text\": \"50 years.\"}]"
  },
  "7YL5SVVXHCo": {
    "video_id": "7YL5SVVXHCo",
    "title": "Trump unloads on Bannon, says he lost his mind (ASL - 1.3.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180104",
    "duration": 142,
    "view_count": 87,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.96, \"end\": 6.84, \"text\": \"A new book entitled \\\"Fire and Fury\\\" was just released.\"}, {\"start\": 6.86, \"end\": 22.06, \"text\": \"A copy of the book was obtained by the newspaper \\\"The Guardian.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 22.12, \"end\": 38.3, \"text\": \"In the book former White House chief strategist Steve Bannon reportedly said the 2016 meeting\"}, {\"start\": 38.3, \"end\": 50.579, \"text\": \"between Trump campaign officials and a Russian lawyer was \\\"treasonous.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 50.58, \"end\": 56.46, \"text\": \"Bannon told the book's author that they should have immediately called the FBI.\"}, {\"start\": 56.46, \"end\": 78.78, \"text\": \"Jared Kushner, Donald Trump, Jr and then-campaign chairman Paul Manafort were present.\"}, {\"start\": 78.82, \"end\": 84.36, \"text\": \"The Russian lawyer purportedly offered Trump's campaign officials damaging information on\"}, {\"start\": 84.36, \"end\": 89.24, \"text\": \"Hillary Clinton.\"}, {\"start\": 89.24, \"end\": 101.52, \"text\": \"President Trump immediately released a blistering statement slamming Bannon.\"}, {\"start\": 101.52, \"end\": 108.6, \"text\": \"Trump said when Bannon was fired, he not only lost his job, he lost his mind.\"}, {\"start\": 108.6, \"end\": 113.48, \"text\": \"Trump also wrote that Bannon, who led the Trump campaign for a time, had very little\"}, {\"start\": 113.48, \"end\": 117.14, \"text\": \"to do with his election victory.\"}, {\"start\": 117.14, \"end\": 130.84, \"text\": \"He also blamed Bannon for the defeat of Alabama GOP Senate candidate Roy Moore and accused\"}, {\"start\": 130.84, \"end\": 141.22, \"text\": \"Bannon of using his White House job to leak false information.\"}]"
  },
  "z5_VAr9YOTU": {
    "video_id": "z5_VAr9YOTU",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.18.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171219",
    "duration": 532,
    "view_count": 421,
    "description": "December 18, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-AMTRAK TRAIN DERAILMENT\n-TAX VOTE, GOVERNMENT SHUTDOWN LOOM ON CAPITOL HILL\n-TRUMP JUDICIAL NOMINEE WITHDRAWS\n-PHOTOS OF DAMAGE FROM ATLANTA AIRPORT FIRE\n-LAKERS TO RETIRE KOBE BRYANT'S JERSEYS\n-DIDDY WANTS TO BUY THE CAROLINA PANTHERS\n-PRINCESS CHARLOTTE BEGINS PRE-SCHOOL IN JANUARY\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE Our talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.38, \"end\": 7.02, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.02, \"end\": 8.84, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.86, \"end\": 9.98, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 9.98, \"end\": 12.28, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.42, \"end\": 25.64, \"text\": \"Several people are dead after an Amtrak passenger train derailed in Pierce County, Washington.\"}, {\"start\": 25.64, \"end\": 31.58, \"text\": \"The train was heading southbound on its way from Seattle to Portland.\"}, {\"start\": 31.58, \"end\": 37.04, \"text\": \"It was the first day and the first trip for this train.\"}, {\"start\": 37.12, \"end\": 44.3, \"text\": \"There were 77 passengers and seven crew members on the train.\"}, {\"start\": 44.3, \"end\": 50.4, \"text\": \"As the train was passing over the bridge over Interstate 5, the train jumped the tracks.\"}, {\"start\": 50.4, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"Part of the train was left dangling off the bridge.\"}, {\"start\": 53.0, \"end\": 58.84, \"text\": \"A few cars and a semi-truck were on the road below when the train derailed.\"}, {\"start\": 58.88, \"end\": 64.3, \"text\": \"Some of those vehicles were crushed by the train but authorities say no one was killed\"}, {\"start\": 64.3, \"end\": 67.34, \"text\": \"on the ground.\"}, {\"start\": 67.36, \"end\": 73.42, \"text\": \"Officials also say witnesses to the crash did what they could to help until emergency\"}, {\"start\": 73.46, \"end\": 78.3, \"text\": \"workers showed up.\"}, {\"start\": 78.3, \"end\": 85.58, \"text\": \"The National Transportation Safety Board (NTSB) sent 20 investigators from Washington DC to\"}, {\"start\": 85.58, \"end\": 90.5, \"text\": \"Washington State to investigate the cause of the derailment.\"}, {\"start\": 90.5, \"end\": 94.94, \"text\": \"Amtrak officials gave a telephone number for people looking for information on family members\"}, {\"start\": 95.0, \"end\": 99.14, \"text\": \"who may have been on the train.\"}, {\"start\": 99.14, \"end\": 106.96, \"text\": \"The number is 1-800-523-9101.\"}, {\"start\": 107.98, \"end\": 110.94, \"text\": \"The clock is ticking on Capitol Hill.\"}, {\"start\": 110.94, \"end\": 116.44, \"text\": \"Congressional Republicans are eager to pass the tax reform bill before heading home for\"}, {\"start\": 116.44, \"end\": 119.76, \"text\": \"the holiday break.\"}, {\"start\": 119.8, \"end\": 127.34, \"text\": \"Early indications point to the tax reform bill passing both the House and Senate this\"}, {\"start\": 127.34, \"end\": 131.1, \"text\": \"week and then heading to President Trump's desk.\"}, {\"start\": 131.1, \"end\": 134.32, \"text\": \"But they also have to come up with a way to avoid a government shutdown\"}, {\"start\": 134.32, \"end\": 135.12, \"text\": \"before midnight Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 135.12, \"end\": 139.56, \"text\": \"A spending bill needs to be passed by midnight Friday to keep the\"}, {\"start\": 139.56, \"end\": 141.98, \"text\": \"federal government up and running.\"}, {\"start\": 141.98, \"end\": 146.0, \"text\": \"Republicans want more defense spending while\"}, {\"start\": 146.0, \"end\": 151.5, \"text\": \"Democrats want more money for domestic programs\"}, {\"start\": 151.5, \"end\": 155.08, \"text\": \"and a deal on the DACA program for young undocumented immigrants.\"}, {\"start\": 155.08, \"end\": 159.96, \"text\": \"Most lawmakers anticipate another short-term resolution to avert a Friday shutdown rather\"}, {\"start\": 159.96, \"end\": 166.28, \"text\": \"than a comprehensive bill.\"}, {\"start\": 166.32, \"end\": 172.88, \"text\": \"Congressional aides expect members to stick around until late Friday\"}, {\"start\": 172.92, \"end\": 177.24, \"text\": \"to get everything done.\"}, {\"start\": 179.0, \"end\": 192.88, \"text\": \"Matthew Petersen, President Trump's District Court nominee, has withdrawn his nomination.\"}, {\"start\": 192.9, \"end\": 198.98, \"text\": \"Peterson was up for a lifetime appointment on the US District Court for the District\"}, {\"start\": 198.98, \"end\": 207.74, \"text\": \"of Columbia but he struggled to answer basic questions during an exchange with Louisiana\"}, {\"start\": 207.74, \"end\": 213.68, \"text\": \"Senator John Kennedy.\"}, {\"start\": 213.68, \"end\": 221.28, \"text\": \"The exchange went viral after a link of the video was tweeted.\"}, {\"start\": 221.52, \"end\": 229.24, \"text\": \"A White House official says Trump has accepted Petersen's decision to withdraw his nomination.\"}, {\"start\": 231.24, \"end\": 236.56, \"text\": \"Here's a look at some of the damage from the fire that knocked out\"}, {\"start\": 236.56, \"end\": 244.64, \"text\": \"power to Atlanta's Hartsfield-Jackson International airport.\"}, {\"start\": 244.76, \"end\": 251.88, \"text\": \"Atlanta's mayor said the outage started with a fire in a Georgia Power\"}, {\"start\": 251.88, \"end\": 258.68, \"text\": \"underground electrical facility.\"}, {\"start\": 258.68, \"end\": 265.6, \"text\": \"He said the electrical fire's intensity damaged two substations serving the airport, including\"}, {\"start\": 265.8, \"end\": 284.0, \"text\": \"the airport's \\\"redundant system\\\" that should have provided backup power.\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 290.24, \"text\": \"The outage lasted nearly 11 hours until late Sunday night.\"}, {\"start\": 290.24, \"end\": 294.6, \"text\": \"It left thousands stranded in dark terminals\"}, {\"start\": 294.68, \"end\": 299.64, \"text\": \"and on planes sitting on the tarmac.\"}, {\"start\": 299.72, \"end\": 305.8, \"text\": \"The ground stop disrupted air travel across the\"}, {\"start\": 305.8, \"end\": 312.64, \"text\": \"U-S and led to cancellations of more than a thousand flights in and out of the airport.\"}, {\"start\": 314.16, \"end\": 335.36, \"text\": \"Tonight the Los Angeles Lakers will retire both of NBA star Kobe Bryant's jerseys.\"}, {\"start\": 335.44, \"end\": 344.56, \"text\": \"The Lakers host the Golden State Warriors at the Staples Center tonight.\"}, {\"start\": 344.56, \"end\": 353.2, \"text\": \"At a special halftime ceremony Bryant's number 27 jersey and his original number 8 jersey\"}, {\"start\": 353.28, \"end\": 355.32, \"text\": \"will be raised to the rafters.\"}, {\"start\": 355.32, \"end\": 362.52, \"text\": \"The historic honor marks the first time an NBA player has had two jerseys retired by\"}, {\"start\": 362.64, \"end\": 366.04, \"text\": \"the same team.\"}, {\"start\": 366.04, \"end\": 373.6, \"text\": \"Bryant retired in 2010 after a 20 year career.\"}, {\"start\": 374.8, \"end\": 385.56, \"text\": \"Today hip-hop producer and entrepreneur Sean \\\"Diddy\\\" Combs tweeted\"}, {\"start\": 385.56, \"end\": 390.48, \"text\": \"that he wants to buy the Carolina Panthers.\"}, {\"start\": 390.48, \"end\": 398.24, \"text\": \"He also posted on Instagram why he would be the best NFL owner.\"}, {\"start\": 398.24, \"end\": 411.16, \"text\": \"Diddy he says if he gets the team, he will immediately hire Colin Kaepernick as quarterback.\"}, {\"start\": 411.16, \"end\": 418.88, \"text\": \"He also said the team will have the best halftime show, the best selection of music and the\"}, {\"start\": 418.88, \"end\": 425.24, \"text\": \"team will win Super Bowl after Super Bowl.\"}, {\"start\": 425.24, \"end\": 435.32, \"text\": \"Diddy has plenty of support, including from NBA star Steph Curry, who tweeted\"}, {\"start\": 435.32, \"end\": 437.88, \"text\": \"he \\\"wants in\\\" on the plan.\"}, {\"start\": 437.88, \"end\": 447.48, \"text\": \"Current Panthers owner, Jerry Richardson, announced plans to sell the team at the end\"}, {\"start\": 447.48, \"end\": 449.64, \"text\": \"of the season.\"}, {\"start\": 449.72, \"end\": 456.64, \"text\": \"Richardson is facing allegations of workplace misconduct.\"}, {\"start\": 457.64, \"end\": 465.8, \"text\": \"On Monday Prince William and Kate Middleton announced their two-year-old daughter,\"}, {\"start\": 465.8, \"end\": 472.24, \"text\": \"Princess Charlotte, will start preschool next month.\"}, {\"start\": 472.24, \"end\": 479.12, \"text\": \"She will attend Willcocks Nursery School.\"}, {\"start\": 479.12, \"end\": 484.64, \"text\": \"The London school is located near the family's home.\"}, {\"start\": 484.64, \"end\": 491.32, \"text\": \"In a statement, the school says it is looking forward to welcoming Charlotte to its nursery.\"}, {\"start\": 491.32, \"end\": 498.479, \"text\": \"On its website, Willcocks describes itself as a school that encourages kids to learn\"}, {\"start\": 498.48, \"end\": 502.96, \"text\": \"to read, write and understand simple numbers with little pressure.\"}, {\"start\": 502.96, \"end\": 508.08, \"text\": \"The school also says its students enjoy lots of playtime.\"}, {\"start\": 509.2, \"end\": 510.92, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 510.92, \"end\": 512.28, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 512.28, \"end\": 514.4, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 514.4, \"end\": 518.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 518.0, \"end\": 523.56, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "h7nmZ1UqNoA": {
    "video_id": "h7nmZ1UqNoA",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.4.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180305",
    "duration": 451,
    "view_count": 1173,
    "description": "3.4.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-“Bomb cyclone” kills six, 900K without power\n-Update: White House shooter dies\n-Michigan murder suspect apprehended\n-500+ officers at Oscars ceremony\n-Girl can’t stop staring at Michelle Obama’s portrait\n-Topless woman protests Italian elections\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Lang",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.3, \"end\": 9.04, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.04, \"end\": 10.86, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.86, \"end\": 12.62, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.62, \"end\": 15.68, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.58, \"end\": 32.02, \"text\": \"The \\\"bomb cyclone\\\" that hammered the Northeast this weekend has now moved out to sea but\"}, {\"start\": 32.02, \"end\": 33.82, \"text\": \"it left a lot of devastation behind.\"}, {\"start\": 33.82, \"end\": 40.94, \"text\": \"The storm killed at least six people and more than 600,000 people from Virginia to Massachusetts\"}, {\"start\": 40.94, \"end\": 43.86, \"text\": \"are without power.\"}, {\"start\": 43.86, \"end\": 51.28, \"text\": \"At one point, homes and buildings in the Boston area were completely underwater.\"}, {\"start\": 51.28, \"end\": 59.28, \"text\": \"In the nearby town of Quincy, police say they performed more than 250 rescues Friday and\"}, {\"start\": 59.28, \"end\": 61.5, \"text\": \"Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 61.54, \"end\": 68.84, \"text\": \"The storm also dumped heavy snow from Ohio to New England and into upstate New York,\"}, {\"start\": 68.84, \"end\": 71.4, \"text\": \"where more than 3 feet of snow was recorded.\"}, {\"start\": 71.4, \"end\": 77.06, \"text\": \"Massachusetts, Virginia and Maryland have issued emergency declaration.\"}, {\"start\": 77.12, \"end\": 83.12, \"text\": \"That allows state and local agencies to help those affected by the storm.\"}, {\"start\": 83.12, \"end\": 92.98, \"text\": \"Nearly 15 million people remained under a coastal flooding warning Saturday afternoon.\"}, {\"start\": 95.88, \"end\": 101.06, \"text\": \"The man who shot himself just outside the White House Saturday morning has died from\"}, {\"start\": 101.06, \"end\": 103.3, \"text\": \"his injuries.\"}, {\"start\": 103.3, \"end\": 109.46, \"text\": \"According to the Secret Service, the incident happened just outside the north fence of the\"}, {\"start\": 109.5, \"end\": 111.68, \"text\": \"building.\"}, {\"start\": 111.68, \"end\": 115.54, \"text\": \"Officials say a man pulled out a gun and fired several rounds.\"}, {\"start\": 115.54, \"end\": 121.82, \"text\": \"None of the shots appeared to be directed at the White House and no Secret Service officers\"}, {\"start\": 121.82, \"end\": 123.5, \"text\": \"returned fire.\"}, {\"start\": 123.5, \"end\": 127.78, \"text\": \"The shooter then turned the gun on himself shot himself in the head.\"}, {\"start\": 127.78, \"end\": 135.4, \"text\": \"Investigators say they did not find a suicide note on the scene but they recovered a book\"}, {\"start\": 135.4, \"end\": 140.88, \"text\": \"that contained some incoherent sentences.\"}, {\"start\": 140.88, \"end\": 149.12, \"text\": \"President Trump and First Lady Melania Trump were at Mar-a-Lago in Florida at the time\"}, {\"start\": 149.12, \"end\": 150.98, \"text\": \"of the incident.\"}, {\"start\": 154.36, \"end\": 169.76, \"text\": \"Central Michigan University police say they have James Eric Davis, Jr. in custody.\"}, {\"start\": 169.76, \"end\": 181.64, \"text\": \"He is the 19-year-old college student accused of shooting and killing his parents in a campus\"}, {\"start\": 181.68, \"end\": 184.22, \"text\": \"dormitory Friday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 184.22, \"end\": 189.16, \"text\": \"They had come to pick him up for spring break.\"}, {\"start\": 189.16, \"end\": 193.28, \"text\": \"Police say Davis shot his parents with his father's gun.\"}, {\"start\": 193.28, \"end\": 197.96, \"text\": \"After the shooting Davis fled.\"}, {\"start\": 197.96, \"end\": 206.84, \"text\": \"But on Sunday, just after midnight, a train operator spotted Davis walking along the tracks\"}, {\"start\": 206.84, \"end\": 209.1, \"text\": \"and called police.\"}, {\"start\": 209.1, \"end\": 213.54, \"text\": \"Within two minutes, police were on the scene and Davis was taken into custody.\"}, {\"start\": 213.54, \"end\": 219.48, \"text\": \"He's been charged with two counts of murder.\"}, {\"start\": 219.48, \"end\": 227.78, \"text\": \"At this point, police have not released a motive for the killings.\"}, {\"start\": 231.48, \"end\": 244.12, \"text\": \"According to Variety magazine, more than 500 officers will be deployed to the Dolby Theater\"}, {\"start\": 244.12, \"end\": 247.6, \"text\": \"for tonight's Oscars ceremony.\"}, {\"start\": 247.6, \"end\": 258.64, \"text\": \"The operation will include the FBI, firefighters, private security guards and police helicopters.\"}, {\"start\": 258.64, \"end\": 265.18, \"text\": \"Variety says the LAPD is extra cautious because of last year's mass shooting in Las Vegas,\"}, {\"start\": 265.18, \"end\": 271.98, \"text\": \"where a gunman opened fire from a hotel.\"}, {\"start\": 271.98, \"end\": 281.18, \"text\": \"But officials say they're not aware of any specific threats against the Academy Awards.\"}, {\"start\": 286.26, \"end\": 294.78, \"text\": \"This photo went viral this week.\"}, {\"start\": 294.78, \"end\": 303.72, \"text\": \"It was taken at the National Portrait Gallery by a visitor from North Carolina who posted\"}, {\"start\": 303.72, \"end\": 305.31, \"text\": \"it on his Facebook page.\"}, {\"start\": 305.31, \"end\": 316.18, \"text\": \"It shows two-year-old Parker Curry staring in awe at a towering portrait of former First\"}, {\"start\": 316.18, \"end\": 323.26, \"text\": \"Lady Michelle Obama.\"}, {\"start\": 323.26, \"end\": 330.82, \"text\": \"Parker's mother said the little girl was so amazed, she wouldn't even turn around for a picture.\"}, {\"start\": 330.82, \"end\": 337.64, \"text\": \"The mother says that Parker believes Michelle Obama is a queen and Parker wants to be a\"}, {\"start\": 337.64, \"end\": 340.86, \"text\": \"queen as well.\"}, {\"start\": 344.06, \"end\": 350.84, \"text\": \"Voting is underway in Italy's unpredictable national election.\"}, {\"start\": 350.84, \"end\": 358.7, \"text\": \"The campaign has been divisive with the issue of immigration front and center.\"}, {\"start\": 358.72, \"end\": 369.48, \"text\": \"Traditional parties on the right and the left are losing ground.\"}, {\"start\": 369.48, \"end\": 379.7, \"text\": \"The Populist Five Star Movement is likely to emerge as the single largest party.\"}, {\"start\": 379.7, \"end\": 389.5, \"text\": \"But no party or group is expected to win the majority needed to form a government.\"}, {\"start\": 389.5, \"end\": 396.24, \"text\": \"There have been protests but none stranger than the one today.\"}, {\"start\": 396.24, \"end\": 407.86, \"text\": \"As former prime minister Silvio Berlusconi was casting his vote for the center-right\"}, {\"start\": 407.86, \"end\": 413.3, \"text\": \"party, a woman popped up from a group of photographers and took off her shirt to reveal\"}, {\"start\": 413.3, \"end\": 420.3, \"text\": \"her bare chest with the words \\\"Berlusconi you are finished!\\\" written on her skin in Italian.\"}, {\"start\": 420.3, \"end\": 423.58, \"text\": \"Berlusconi did not acknowledge the woman's protest and instead walked out of the precinct.\"}, {\"start\": 425.62, \"end\": 428.6, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 428.6, \"end\": 430.1, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 430.1, \"end\": 432.44, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 432.44, \"end\": 436.9, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 436.9, \"end\": 443.22, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "5gFYtIKARVg": {
    "video_id": "5gFYtIKARVg",
    "title": "DPN 30 year anniversary (ASL - 3.6.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180307",
    "duration": 131,
    "view_count": 153,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.64, \"end\": 7.12, \"text\": \"Today marks a groundbreaking day in Deaf history and American history.\"}, {\"start\": 7.12, \"end\": 14.5, \"text\": \"Thirty years ago students at Gallaudet University kicked off a massive protest, demanding the\"}, {\"start\": 14.5, \"end\": 16.86, \"text\": \"school appoint a Deaf president.\"}, {\"start\": 16.86, \"end\": 24.34, \"text\": \"When the board hired a hearing person instead, the students became livid!\"}, {\"start\": 24.34, \"end\": 28.76, \"text\": \"What happened next was a weeklong protest that made news all around the world.\"}, {\"start\": 28.76, \"end\": 34.3, \"text\": \"\\\"Deaf President Now\\\" became the rallying cry and the protest made its way all the way to\"}, {\"start\": 34.3, \"end\": 38.6, \"text\": \"Capitol Hill.\"}, {\"start\": 38.6, \"end\": 44.14, \"text\": \"Eventually the board conceded and I. King Jordan was named Gallaudet's as first Deaf\"}, {\"start\": 44.14, \"end\": 45.94, \"text\": \"president.\"}, {\"start\": 45.94, \"end\": 56.22, \"text\": \"Two weeks ago Gallaudet's board announced an official resolution marking March 6th-13th\"}, {\"start\": 56.22, \"end\": 58.34, \"text\": \"as \\\"DPN Week.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 58.36, \"end\": 65.78, \"text\": \"Yesterday Sign1News anchor Candace Jones spoke with the four student-leaders who led the\"}, {\"start\": 65.78, \"end\": 82.9, \"text\": \"protest 30 years ago: Jerry Covell, Tim Rarus, Bridgetta Bourne and Greg Hlibok.\"}, {\"start\": 82.9, \"end\": 90.78, \"text\": \"Hlibok explains why this week is so important for the younger generation.\"}, {\"start\": 92.36, \"end\": 102.42, \"text\": \"It's important for us to recognize DPN, to celebrate and cherish it as part of our Deaf history.\"}, {\"start\": 102.5, \"end\": 114.02, \"text\": \"More and more young people don't know the history of DPN and the impact that it had.\"}, {\"start\": 114.02, \"end\": 121.32, \"text\": \"We won't be around forever so we have to passed down that history.\"}, {\"start\": 122.34, \"end\": 126.8, \"text\": \"If you missed the live interview with the DPN leaders, just head to our Facebook page\"}, {\"start\": 126.8, \"end\": 128.96, \"text\": \"and you can see it in its entirety.\"}]"
  },
  "Y86eXzDlorE": {
    "video_id": "Y86eXzDlorE",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.12.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180212",
    "duration": 677,
    "view_count": 1907,
    "description": "2.12.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Oxfam deputy chief resigns over sex crimes scandal\n-California launches Aetna investigation\n-Facebook losing younger users to snapchat at fast pace\n-The official Obama portraits unveiled\n-Prince Harry, Meghan Markle new wedding details\n-Overturned truck sparks unbelievable fireball\n-Dogs take over Manhattan for Westminster\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with w",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.94, \"end\": 9.34, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.34, \"end\": 11.2, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.2, \"end\": 12.92, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.92, \"end\": 16.32, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.08, \"end\": 31.02, \"text\": \"Oxfam's deputy chief executive, Penny Lawrence, has resigned amid a growing sex crimes scandal\"}, {\"start\": 31.02, \"end\": 39.739, \"text\": \"involving the organization's aid workers in Haiti and Chad.\"}, {\"start\": 39.74, \"end\": 54.3, \"text\": \"Oxfam is one of the UK's largest and most prominent aid organizations.\"}, {\"start\": 54.3, \"end\": 62.38, \"text\": \"An investigation by the Times newspaper in London revealed allegations that Oxfam's leaders\"}, {\"start\": 62.399, \"end\": 70.25, \"text\": \"tried to cover up sex crimes by senior employees after the devastating 2010 quake, which killed\"}, {\"start\": 70.25, \"end\": 78.38, \"text\": \"hundreds of thousands of people.\"}, {\"start\": 78.38, \"end\": 84.18, \"text\": \"The aid workers are accused of turning a villa rented by the organization into a makeshift\"}, {\"start\": 84.26, \"end\": 93.2, \"text\": \"brothel and hiring prostitutes to wear only Oxfam t-shirts.\"}, {\"start\": 93.2, \"end\": 99.88, \"text\": \"Some Oxfam staff are accused of paying sex workers in Chad as well.\"}, {\"start\": 99.88, \"end\": 105.02, \"text\": \"Officials with the organization did not deny the accusations against its staff members\"}, {\"start\": 105.02, \"end\": 109.9, \"text\": \"but they do deny trying to cover it up, saying it launched a swift investigation which resulted\"}, {\"start\": 109.9, \"end\": 113.64, \"text\": \"in four people being fired and three resigning.\"}, {\"start\": 113.66, \"end\": 123.24, \"text\": \"The British government is now threatening to pull tens of millions in funding as a result\"}, {\"start\": 123.24, \"end\": 125.52, \"text\": \"of the scandal.\"}, {\"start\": 125.52, \"end\": 131.06, \"text\": \"Haiti is considering criminal charges against the workers.\"}, {\"start\": 135.08, \"end\": 142.88, \"text\": \"California is launching an investigation into insurance giant Aetna.\"}, {\"start\": 142.88, \"end\": 155.82, \"text\": \"It's because former medical director Dr. Jay Ken Iinuma admitted under oath that he never\"}, {\"start\": 155.82, \"end\": 162.0, \"text\": \"looked at patients' records before denying or approving care.\"}, {\"start\": 162.0, \"end\": 170.4, \"text\": \"Now that's leading to questions about Aetna's practice nationwide.\"}, {\"start\": 170.4, \"end\": 181.36, \"text\": \"And the acknowledgment by Dr. Iinuma is a cornerstone of a lawsuit against Aetna by\"}, {\"start\": 181.36, \"end\": 186.62, \"text\": \"a young man named Gillen Washington.\"}, {\"start\": 186.62, \"end\": 192.36, \"text\": \"Washington has a serious immune deficiency.\"}, {\"start\": 192.36, \"end\": 198.6, \"text\": \"Aetna initially paid for Washington's treatments after services were rendered.\"}, {\"start\": 198.6, \"end\": 209.04, \"text\": \"But in 2014, Iinuma did not pre-approved payment for Washington to have treatment.\"}, {\"start\": 209.04, \"end\": 217.88, \"text\": \"Without treatment, Washington became sicker and sicker, ending up in the intensive care\"}, {\"start\": 217.88, \"end\": 220.86, \"text\": \"unit with a collapsed lung.\"}, {\"start\": 220.86, \"end\": 229.24, \"text\": \"Responding to the investigation, an Aetna spokesman told CNN: \\\"Aetna medical directors\"}, {\"start\": 229.24, \"end\": 239.06, \"text\": \"are trained to review all available medical information, including medical records, to\"}, {\"start\": 239.06, \"end\": 248.88, \"text\": \"make an informed decision, adding that medical directors take their duties and responsibilities\"}, {\"start\": 248.88, \"end\": 251.78, \"text\": \"as medical professionals incredibly seriously.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 251.78, \"end\": 261.68, \"text\": \"The company also said Iinuma's tenure ended in 2015.\"}, {\"start\": 265.08, \"end\": 281.58, \"text\": \"According to a new study from Emarketer, Facebook is losing young users to Snapchat at an even\"}, {\"start\": 281.64, \"end\": 286.54, \"text\": \"faster pace than previously thought.\"}, {\"start\": 286.54, \"end\": 296.24, \"text\": \"The study says less than half of US internet users ages 12 to 17 will use Facebook this year.\"}, {\"start\": 296.24, \"end\": 304.8, \"text\": \"That means Facebook will lose 2 million users under 25 this year.\"}, {\"start\": 304.8, \"end\": 316.02, \"text\": \"And the social media giant can no longer depend on Instagram to help retain the younger audience.\"}, {\"start\": 316.02, \"end\": 327.2, \"text\": \"The study found that Instagram will add 1.6 million young users this year while Snapchat\"}, {\"start\": 327.2, \"end\": 334.94, \"text\": \"will add 1.9 million and continues to add more users ages 12 to 14 than Instagram.\"}, {\"start\": 334.94, \"end\": 343.88, \"text\": \"Facebook is still the world's most popular online hangout with 2 billion users, but its\"}, {\"start\": 343.88, \"end\": 349.72, \"text\": \"growth is mostly being driven by older adult users.\"}, {\"start\": 349.72, \"end\": 359.26, \"text\": \"Researchers say teens prefer the instant gratification of Snapchat and feel like Facebook is too much\"}, {\"start\": 359.26, \"end\": 362.28, \"text\": \"of an investment of their time.\"}, {\"start\": 365.42, \"end\": 380.92, \"text\": \"Barack and Michelle Obama's official portraits were unveiled at the Smithsonian's National\"}, {\"start\": 380.92, \"end\": 384.36, \"text\": \"Portrait Gallery today in Washington DC.\"}, {\"start\": 384.36, \"end\": 391.18, \"text\": \"This is a rite of passage for most former presidents, all of whom have their portraits\"}, {\"start\": 391.18, \"end\": 394.14, \"text\": \"hanging in the museum.\"}, {\"start\": 394.14, \"end\": 401.94, \"text\": \"The unveiling of these particular portraits was greatly anticipated because of the artists\"}, {\"start\": 401.94, \"end\": 404.8, \"text\": \"the Obamas selected.\"}, {\"start\": 404.8, \"end\": 415.74, \"text\": \"The former president chose Kehinde Wiley, a Yale University-trained painter.\"}, {\"start\": 415.74, \"end\": 421.56, \"text\": \"Wiley is the first African-American artist to paint an official presidential portrait\"}, {\"start\": 421.56, \"end\": 426.18, \"text\": \"for the National Portrait Gallery.\"}, {\"start\": 426.18, \"end\": 435.62, \"text\": \"The former First Lady chose Baltimore-based African-American artist Amy Sherald.\"}, {\"start\": 435.62, \"end\": 445.1, \"text\": \"Barack Obama's portrait will hang in the Hall of Presidents and Michelle Obama's portrait\"}, {\"start\": 445.1, \"end\": 448.54, \"text\": \"will be placed in the museum's \\\"Recent Acquisitions\\\" corridor.\"}, {\"start\": 448.56, \"end\": 456.0, \"text\": \"Both will be open for public viewing on Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 459.2, \"end\": 471.28, \"text\": \"Kensington Palace has announced new details about the wedding of Prince Harry and Meghan\"}, {\"start\": 471.28, \"end\": 473.76, \"text\": \"Markle.\"}, {\"start\": 473.76, \"end\": 478.96, \"text\": \"The couple will marry at noon local time on May 19th.\"}, {\"start\": 478.96, \"end\": 483.68, \"text\": \"That's 7 AM Eastern in the US.\"}, {\"start\": 483.76, \"end\": 493.52, \"text\": \"The wedding will take place in St. George's Chapel at Windsor Castle.\"}, {\"start\": 493.52, \"end\": 501.44, \"text\": \"The palace also announced the couple will undertake a carriage procession.\"}, {\"start\": 501.44, \"end\": 508.0, \"text\": \"The carriage will go through the town of Windsor and then returned to the castle.\"}, {\"start\": 508.0, \"end\": 515.92, \"text\": \"The couple will also hold their wedding reception in Windsor Castle with the Prince of Wales\"}, {\"start\": 515.92, \"end\": 524.8, \"text\": \"hosting a private party for close friends and family later in the evening.\"}, {\"start\": 528.24, \"end\": 537.52, \"text\": \"A truck loaded with liquefied natural gas overturned in China and sparked any enormous\"}, {\"start\": 537.52, \"end\": 540.42, \"text\": \"explosion.\"}, {\"start\": 540.42, \"end\": 543.92, \"text\": \"The fireball spread incredibly fast and engulfed, not only the vehicle, but trees lining the\"}, {\"start\": 543.92, \"end\": 546.34, \"text\": \"roadway.\"}, {\"start\": 546.4, \"end\": 549.62, \"text\": \"You have to see the video to believe it.\"}, {\"start\": 549.62, \"end\": 550.82, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 571.72, \"end\": 578.84, \"text\": \"Two people were rushed to the hospital with burns and other injuries.\"}, {\"start\": 578.84, \"end\": 589.86, \"text\": \"Several other cars were burned nearby but the occupants escaped unharmed.\"}, {\"start\": 589.86, \"end\": 592.98, \"text\": \"Wow!\"}, {\"start\": 596.28, \"end\": 607.68, \"text\": \"More than 2,800 perfectly poised pooches are in Manhattan ready to strut their stuff at\"}, {\"start\": 607.8, \"end\": 610.18, \"text\": \"the Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show.\"}, {\"start\": 610.18, \"end\": 616.1, \"text\": \"This is the country's most prestigious dog competition.\"}, {\"start\": 616.1, \"end\": 623.22, \"text\": \"This year's show coincides with the Chinese new year and 2018 just happens to be the Year\"}, {\"start\": 623.22, \"end\": 625.26, \"text\": \"of the Dog.\"}, {\"start\": 625.28, \"end\": 640.0, \"text\": \"Dogs will be judged on grooming and the crowd-favorite agility competition.\"}, {\"start\": 640.0, \"end\": 648.76, \"text\": \"That all leads up to see who is going to be named \\\"Best In Show\\\" Tuesday night.\"}, {\"start\": 652.62, \"end\": 655.02, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 655.02, \"end\": 656.4, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 656.4, \"end\": 658.6, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 658.6, \"end\": 662.94, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 662.96, \"end\": 669.24, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "FZ-o3FNEVnA": {
    "video_id": "FZ-o3FNEVnA",
    "title": "Sign1News 6.1.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180601",
    "duration": 541,
    "view_count": 1147,
    "description": "6.1.18 - \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Hurricane season beings today, be prepared\n-Suspect in deputy murder captured\n-Woman amend Crystal Methuen busted for crystal meth\n-Roseanne says she begged ABC to save her show\n-Should Samantha Bee be fired over Trump slur?\n-World’s oldest woman turns 129\n-Soldiers welcome baby of fallen hero\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides eq",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.16, \"end\": 9.34, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.38, \"end\": 10.92, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.92, \"end\": 12.56, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.56, \"end\": 15.14, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.24, \"end\": 25.78, \"text\": \"The 2018 Atlantic hurricane season starts today.\"}, {\"start\": 25.78, \"end\": 34.04, \"text\": \"Officials are warning people to hope for the best but prepare for the worst.\"}, {\"start\": 34.04, \"end\": 42.4, \"text\": \"We've already had one named tropical storm this year, Alberto, and that storm system\"}, {\"start\": 42.4, \"end\": 46.1, \"text\": \"is still wreaking and destruction on the East Coast.\"}, {\"start\": 46.1, \"end\": 56.0, \"text\": \"The National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration is predicting a normal to above-average season.\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 61.74, \"text\": \"Forecasters say we could see 10 to 16 named storms.\"}, {\"start\": 61.74, \"end\": 67.98, \"text\": \"Out of those, they say 5 to 9 of those could become hurricanes and 1 to 4 could become\"}, {\"start\": 67.98, \"end\": 75.52, \"text\": \"major hurricanes, which means Category 3 strength or higher.\"}, {\"start\": 75.52, \"end\": 79.42, \"text\": \"One predictable thing about hurricanes is they are unpredictable so officials stressed\"}, {\"start\": 79.42, \"end\": 83.2, \"text\": \"the importance of being prepared.\"}, {\"start\": 83.2, \"end\": 91.34, \"text\": \"They say take this hurricane season seriously and make an emergency plan for you and your family.\"}, {\"start\": 91.34, \"end\": 96.52, \"text\": \"That includes updating emergency supply kits with food, medicine, cash and important documents\"}, {\"start\": 96.52, \"end\": 104.2, \"text\": \"like driver's license, passport, birth certificate, mortgage or lease agreements and insurance\"}, {\"start\": 104.2, \"end\": 110.44, \"text\": \"information.\"}, {\"start\": 110.44, \"end\": 116.92, \"text\": \"Checklists of information about preparing for disasters like hurricanes can be found\"}, {\"start\": 116.92, \"end\": 118.56, \"text\": \"at Ready.gov.\"}, {\"start\": 120.08, \"end\": 127.64, \"text\": \"Last night we told you about a nationwide manhunt for Steven Wiggins.\"}, {\"start\": 127.64, \"end\": 137.24, \"text\": \"He is the man accused in the shooting death of Dickson County Sgt. Daniel Baker.\"}, {\"start\": 137.24, \"end\": 147.32, \"text\": \"Authorities say Wiggins shot Baker to death during a call about a suspicious vehicle.\"}, {\"start\": 147.32, \"end\": 155.16, \"text\": \"Today the Tennessee Bureau of Investigation tweeted these photos of Wiggins handcuffs\"}, {\"start\": 155.32, \"end\": 157.92, \"text\": \"in the back of a patrol car.\"}, {\"start\": 157.92, \"end\": 163.0, \"text\": \"Wiggins is now charged with premeditated murder.\"}, {\"start\": 163.0, \"end\": 170.76, \"text\": \"The Dickson County District Attorney's Office will seek the death penalty against Wiggins.\"}, {\"start\": 174.04, \"end\": 185.56, \"text\": \"In St. Augustine, Florida police have arrested this woman for alleged possession of crystal meth.\"}, {\"start\": 185.56, \"end\": 190.96, \"text\": \"And we know you're saying \\\"Okay, so what?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 190.96, \"end\": 197.4, \"text\": \"Well, the woman's name is Crystal Methvin.\"}, {\"start\": 197.4, \"end\": 206.44, \"text\": \"Authorities say an anonymous tip led police to a parking lot where Methvin and two other\"}, {\"start\": 206.44, \"end\": 211.36, \"text\": \"people were caught with a substance revealed to be crystal meth.\"}, {\"start\": 211.36, \"end\": 219.64, \"text\": \"We have also learned that Methvin has a long arrest record going back to 1998.\"}, {\"start\": 219.64, \"end\": 226.12, \"text\": \"She's been arrested at least nine times on drug charges in the last two decades.\"}, {\"start\": 228.6, \"end\": 233.28, \"text\": \"Roseanne Barr is back on Twitter again.\"}, {\"start\": 233.28, \"end\": 241.92, \"text\": \"In a series of tweets Thursday, Barr said she begged Ben Sherwood, the president of\"}, {\"start\": 241.92, \"end\": 250.44, \"text\": \"Disney-ABC television group, to keep her show on the air.\"}, {\"start\": 250.44, \"end\": 258.36, \"text\": \"Barr says she was willing to do whatever her boss wanted but those efforts were in vain\"}, {\"start\": 258.36, \"end\": 261.88, \"text\": \"and the show was yanked.\"}, {\"start\": 261.88, \"end\": 272.48, \"text\": \"Over Memorial Day weekend Barr tweeted a series of racist comments about former Obama aide\"}, {\"start\": 272.48, \"end\": 275.04, \"text\": \"Valerie Jarrett.\"}, {\"start\": 275.04, \"end\": 282.08, \"text\": \"Barr deleted the tweet and apologize shortly afterwards but the damage was already done.\"}, {\"start\": 283.84, \"end\": 287.72, \"text\": \"We want to warn you: some of the language in this story is explicit.\"}, {\"start\": 287.72, \"end\": 298.32, \"text\": \"Earlier this month comedian Samantha Bee made a derogatory comment about the president's\"}, {\"start\": 298.32, \"end\": 304.04, \"text\": \"daughter, Ivanka, on her TBS show \\\"Full Frontal.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 304.04, \"end\": 310.16, \"text\": \"She called Ivanka a \\\"feckless cunt.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 310.16, \"end\": 316.24, \"text\": \"Many agree her comments were vile and vicious and Bee has apologized, saying she crossed\"}, {\"start\": 316.24, \"end\": 318.12, \"text\": \"the line.\"}, {\"start\": 318.12, \"end\": 320.76, \"text\": \"But should she be fired over it?\"}, {\"start\": 320.76, \"end\": 323.92, \"text\": \"President Trump says yes!\"}, {\"start\": 323.92, \"end\": 331.35, \"text\": \"Friday morning Trump tweeted: \\\"Why aren't they firing no talent Samantha Bee for the\"}, {\"start\": 331.36, \"end\": 335.48, \"text\": \"horrible language used on her low ratings show?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 335.48, \"end\": 344.15, \"text\": \"This week ABC canceled Roseanne Barr's hit sitcom following a racist remark.\"}, {\"start\": 344.16, \"end\": 351.24, \"text\": \"Trump called the controversy with Bee \\\"a total double standard.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 353.12, \"end\": 366.48, \"text\": \"Not many people can say they've lived in three centuries but Koku Istambulova can.\"}, {\"start\": 366.48, \"end\": 370.36, \"text\": \"She might be among the oldest of her generation.\"}, {\"start\": 370.36, \"end\": 375.33, \"text\": \"Her birth certificate says she was born on June 1, 1889.\"}, {\"start\": 375.33, \"end\": 381.08, \"text\": \"That makes today her 129th birthday!\"}, {\"start\": 381.08, \"end\": 390.96, \"text\": \"Growing up in Chechnya, Russia, Istambulova didn't live a leisurely life.\"}, {\"start\": 390.96, \"end\": 398.72, \"text\": \"She grew up working in the fields, harvesting cotton, wheat and corn.\"}, {\"start\": 398.72, \"end\": 410.28, \"text\": \"She was born before the end of Imperial Russia and Tsar Nicholas the Second's assassination.\"}, {\"start\": 410.28, \"end\": 422.04, \"text\": \"When Joseph Stalin exiled the Chechens, most of Istambulova's family died in Central Asia,\"}, {\"start\": 422.04, \"end\": 426.36, \"text\": \"including her two sons.\"}, {\"start\": 426.36, \"end\": 436.92, \"text\": \"Now she lives with her grandson in Chechnya after losing her husband just 10 years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 437.08, \"end\": 441.64, \"text\": \"He also lived into his 120's.\"}, {\"start\": 443.28, \"end\": 453.04, \"text\": \"Two-month-old Christian Harris will never know her father Christopher Harris.\"}, {\"start\": 453.04, \"end\": 460.68, \"text\": \"He was killed while serving in Afghanistan just days after finding out he was going to be a dad.\"}, {\"start\": 460.68, \"end\": 465.92, \"text\": \"Some of the men and women who served alongside Harris and were in the vehicle explosion that\"}, {\"start\": 465.92, \"end\": 475.62, \"text\": \"killed him are now giving his daughter a legacy and a surrogate family.\"}, {\"start\": 475.62, \"end\": 483.0, \"text\": \"They were there to support his widow, Britt Harris, through her pregnancy.\"}, {\"start\": 483.0, \"end\": 494.44, \"text\": \"Members of the 82nd Airborne Division even revealed the baby's gender to her over video in October.\"}, {\"start\": 494.44, \"end\": 500.76, \"text\": \"On Tuesday, Harris gathered her husband's comrades together for special photo shoot\"}, {\"start\": 500.76, \"end\": 503.68, \"text\": \"with Christian.\"}, {\"start\": 503.68, \"end\": 512.8, \"text\": \"The new mom says she hopes Christian inherits her father's extroverted personality and love\"}, {\"start\": 512.8, \"end\": 515.82, \"text\": \"of meeting new people.\"}, {\"start\": 518.52, \"end\": 520.84, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 520.84, \"end\": 522.22, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 522.22, \"end\": 524.12, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 524.12, \"end\": 528.3, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 528.36, \"end\": 529.72, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 529.8, \"end\": 530.7, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 530.7, \"end\": 533.68, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "iZq3yQQ07s0": {
    "video_id": "iZq3yQQ07s0",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.12.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171013",
    "duration": 648,
    "view_count": 196,
    "description": "October 12, 2017\nSign1News delivers news for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).\n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-CALIFORNIA WILDFIRES UPDATE\n-TRUMP SIGNS HEALTHCARE EXECUTIVE ORDER\n-TRUMP SLAMMED FOR PUERTO RICO TWEET\n-LAS VEGAS SHOOTING LAWSUIT\n-WEINSTEIN CHECKS INTO REHAB\n-OPHELIA BECOMES 10TH HURRICANE\n-CHILDHOOD OBESITY INCREASING WORLDWIDE\n-DOG WITH THE WORLD'S LONGEST TONGUE\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 13.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Crystal\"}, {\"start\": 13.0, \"end\": 19.0, \"text\": \"Cousineau. And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 25.0, \"end\": 30.0, \"text\": \"In California wildfires continue to burn\"}, {\"start\": 30.0, \"end\": 34.0, \"text\": \"thousands of acres with no end in sight.\"}, {\"start\": 34.0, \"end\": 37.0, \"text\": \"Strong winds, low\"}, {\"start\": 39.0, \"end\": 44.0, \"text\": \"humidity and the absence\"}, {\"start\": 44.0, \"end\": 49.0, \"text\": \"of rain are not helping the fight.\"}, {\"start\": 50.0, \"end\": 55.0, \"text\": \"The death toll is rising now. Twenty-three people\"}, {\"start\": 55.0, \"end\": 60.0, \"text\": \"have been killed and hundreds of families are searching\"}, {\"start\": 60.0, \"end\": 64.0, \"text\": \"desperately for their missing loved ones.\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 69.0, \"text\": \"In Sonoma County, police are going\"}, {\"start\": 71.0, \"end\": 76.0, \"text\": \"door to door warning people to leave.\"}, {\"start\": 77.0, \"end\": 82.0, \"text\": \"In addition to the fire danger, now heavy smoke is\"}, {\"start\": 82.0, \"end\": 86.0, \"text\": \"making it hard for people to breathe and\"}, {\"start\": 86.0, \"end\": 92.0, \"text\": \"it is hampering cell signals.\"}, {\"start\": 96.0, \"end\": 101.0, \"text\": \"Congress failed to pass\"}, {\"start\": 102.0, \"end\": 106.0, \"text\": \"a new healthcare bill so President Trump\"}, {\"start\": 107.0, \"end\": 112.0, \"text\": \"has signed an executive order\"}, {\"start\": 113.0, \"end\": 117.0, \"text\": \"calling on his administration\"}, {\"start\": 118.0, \"end\": 122.0, \"text\": \"to develop policies to\"}, {\"start\": 122.9, \"end\": 128.9, \"text\": \"increase healthcare choices and\"}, {\"start\": 128.9, \"end\": 136.9, \"text\": \"competition among insurance companies.\"}, {\"start\": 137.0, \"end\": 143.0, \"text\": \"Trump says the executive order\"}, {\"start\": 143.0, \"end\": 148.0, \"text\": \"means millions of Americans will\"}, {\"start\": 148.0, \"end\": 152.0, \"text\": \"get a chance to find better\"}, {\"start\": 154.0, \"end\": 156.0, \"text\": \"healthcare options.\"}, {\"start\": 156.0, \"end\": 161.0, \"text\": \"Critics say this executive order could end up\"}, {\"start\": 161.0, \"end\": 166.0, \"text\": \"dismantling Obamacare because younger and\"}, {\"start\": 166.0, \"end\": 170.0, \"text\": \"healthier customers may back away\"}, {\"start\": 170.0, \"end\": 172.0, \"text\": \"from the Affordable Care Act.\"}, {\"start\": 172.0, \"end\": 177.0, \"text\": \"Unfortunately lower costs could mean lower benefits.\"}, {\"start\": 181.0, \"end\": 185.0, \"text\": \"On Thursday President Trump sent out a tweet\"}, {\"start\": 186.0, \"end\": 191.0, \"text\": \"that seemed to suggest that Puerto Rico needs to take\"}, {\"start\": 191.0, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"more responsibility in recovery from Hurricane\"}, {\"start\": 197.0, \"end\": 202.0, \"text\": \"Maria. He blamed Puerto\"}, {\"start\": 202.0, \"end\": 207.0, \"text\": \"Rico for its crumbling infrastructure and financial crisis.\"}, {\"start\": 207.0, \"end\": 211.0, \"text\": \"He said that federal emergency responders\"}, {\"start\": 211.0, \"end\": 216.0, \"text\": \"and the military cannot stay there\"}, {\"start\": 217.0, \"end\": 221.0, \"text\": \"forever. Those comments have\"}, {\"start\": 221.0, \"end\": 226.0, \"text\": \"angered many people. Instead of calling Trump\"}, {\"start\": 227.0, \"end\": 232.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Commander-in-chief\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 232.0, \"end\": 236.0, \"text\": \"the mayor in San Juan\"}, {\"start\": 238.0, \"end\": 243.0, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico called him\"}, {\"start\": 243.0, \"end\": 248.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Hater-in-chief.\\\" And many\"}, {\"start\": 248.0, \"end\": 252.0, \"text\": \"critics noticed Trump did not pull support from\"}, {\"start\": 252.0, \"end\": 257.0, \"text\": \"Texas and Florida.Those states were hit by hurricanes too.\"}, {\"start\": 257.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"But critics also say those states also\"}, {\"start\": 261.124, \"end\": 264.124, \"text\": \"voted for Trump in the election.\"}, {\"start\": 269.0, \"end\": 272.0, \"text\": \"A California college student named Paige\"}, {\"start\": 273.0, \"end\": 278.0, \"text\": \"Gasper, who was injured in the Las Vegas shooting,\"}, {\"start\": 278.0, \"end\": 283.0, \"text\": \"has decided to file a lawsuit against\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 289.0, \"text\": \"MGM Resorts (that's the company\"}, {\"start\": 289.0, \"end\": 293.0, \"text\": \"that owns Mandalay Bay Hotel),\"}, {\"start\": 293.0, \"end\": 297.0, \"text\": \"the concert promoter and a\"}, {\"start\": 297.0, \"end\": 302.0, \"text\": \"gun manufacturer.\"}, {\"start\": 302.0, \"end\": 306.0, \"text\": \"Gasper says that they are all\"}, {\"start\": 307.0, \"end\": 311.0, \"text\": \"liable in the shooting. She says the\"}, {\"start\": 311.0, \"end\": 316.0, \"text\": \"hotel should have noticed the behavior of the gunman before\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 321.0, \"text\": \"he started shooting and failed to respond in a timely manner\"}, {\"start\": 321.0, \"end\": 327.0, \"text\": \"after the shooting started. Gasper says the lawsuit is not about getting money.\"}, {\"start\": 327.0, \"end\": 331.0, \"text\": \"It's about wanting change in business\"}, {\"start\": 332.0, \"end\": 337.0, \"text\": \"practices and making sure everyone is safe.\"}, {\"start\": 342.0, \"end\": 345.0, \"text\": \"At least two shows --\\\"Entertainment\"}, {\"start\": 346.001, \"end\": 349.003, \"text\": \"Tonight\\\" and\"}, {\"start\": 349.2, \"end\": 352.2, \"text\": \"\\\"TMZ\\\" -- are reporting that\"}, {\"start\": 353.0, \"end\": 358.0, \"text\": \"Harvey Weinstein has decided to enter a\"}, {\"start\": 358.0, \"end\": 363.0, \"text\": \"rehab facility in Arizona.\"}, {\"start\": 364.0, \"end\": 368.0, \"text\": \"Dozens of women have come forward accusing\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 374.0, \"text\": \"the Hollywood producer of rape and sexual harassment.\"}, {\"start\": 374.0, \"end\": 380.0, \"text\": \"Now the New York Police Department is investigating the allegations.\"}, {\"start\": 380.0, \"end\": 384.0, \"text\": \"They need to find the women who claim Weinstein\"}, {\"start\": 384.0, \"end\": 391.0, \"text\": \"sexually assaulted them so that they can interview them.\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"Tropical storm Ophelia\"}, {\"start\": 398.0, \"end\": 402.0, \"text\": \"is now a hurricane over the east\"}, {\"start\": 403.0, \"end\": 408.0, \"text\": \"Atlantic. This is the tenth consecutive\"}, {\"start\": 409.0, \"end\": 413.0, \"text\": \"named storm in the Atlantic\"}, {\"start\": 414.0, \"end\": 419.0, \"text\": \"to become a hurricane --tying a record\"}, {\"start\": 420.0, \"end\": 425.0, \"text\": \"set back in the 1800's.\"}, {\"start\": 425.0, \"end\": 429.0, \"text\": \"Ophelia is not a threat to land.\"}, {\"start\": 430.0, \"end\": 435.0, \"text\": \"On Monday the hurricane will approach\"}, {\"start\": 435.0, \"end\": 441.0, \"text\": \"Ireland as a strong extra-tropical storm.\"}, {\"start\": 446.0, \"end\": 451.0, \"text\": \"A new report says the number of\"}, {\"start\": 451.1, \"end\": 455.1, \"text\": \"obese children and adolescents around the world\"}, {\"start\": 455.1, \"end\": 460.1, \"text\": \"is more than 10 times higher than\"}, {\"start\": 460.1, \"end\": 465.1, \"text\": \"40 years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 465.1, \"end\": 466.1, \"text\": \"Last year\"}, {\"start\": 466.101, \"end\": 469.103, \"text\": \"124 million children around\"}, {\"start\": 469.2, \"end\": 474.2, \"text\": \"the world were obese. Another 213 million\"}, {\"start\": 474.2, \"end\": 478.0, \"text\": \"children and adolescents were\"}, {\"start\": 478.0, \"end\": 482.0, \"text\": \"overweight. The rise in obesity\"}, {\"start\": 483.0, \"end\": 491.0, \"text\": \"has accelerated in low and middle income regions\"}, {\"start\": 491.7, \"end\": 499.7, \"text\": \"especially in east and south Asia.\"}, {\"start\": 500.624, \"end\": 504.899, \"text\": \"Being obese as a child can eventually\"}, {\"start\": 504.9, \"end\": 507.9, \"text\": \"lead to increased risk of diabetes,\"}, {\"start\": 508.0, \"end\": 515.0, \"text\": \"cardiovascular disease and some cancers.\"}, {\"start\": 515.0, \"end\": 519.1, \"text\": \"Doctors are hoping that\"}, {\"start\": 520.0, \"end\": 524.0, \"text\": \"their research will generate change.\"}, {\"start\": 525.0, \"end\": 530.0, \"text\": \"They say sugar taxes, restricting marketing of\"}, {\"start\": 530.0, \"end\": 533.0, \"text\": \"unhealthy foods and\"}, {\"start\": 534.0, \"end\": 538.0, \"text\": \"increasing physical activity in schools\"}, {\"start\": 539.0, \"end\": 543.0, \"text\": \"are all effective ways to combat childhood obesity.\"}, {\"start\": 549.024, \"end\": 551.024, \"text\": \"Most dogs have a tendency\"}, {\"start\": 552.0, \"end\": 556.0, \"text\": \"to wag their tails. But this\"}, {\"start\": 557.0, \"end\": 562.0, \"text\": \"one wags her tongue. Meet Mochi.\"}, {\"start\": 562.0, \"end\": 567.0, \"text\": \"She is the Guinness world record holder for\"}, {\"start\": 568.0, \"end\": 572.0, \"text\": \"the dog with the longest tongue. The South Dakota\"}, {\"start\": 572.0, \"end\": 579.0, \"text\": \"St. Bernard's tongue was officially\"}, {\"start\": 579.0, \"end\": 587.0, \"text\": \"measured at 7.3 inches in length.\"}, {\"start\": 587.0, \"end\": 594.0, \"text\": \"Mochi was rescued by her owners when she was 2-years old.\"}, {\"start\": 594.0, \"end\": 599.0, \"text\": \"Now Mochi will star in Guinness's\"}, {\"start\": 600.0, \"end\": 603.0, \"text\": \"upcoming book entitled\"}, {\"start\": 605.0, \"end\": 609.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Amazing Animals.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 611.101, \"end\": 614.103, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories.\"}, {\"start\": 614.2, \"end\": 619.2, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 619.201, \"end\": 622.403, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 622.5, \"end\": 625.5, \"text\": \"Remember to \\\"Like\\\" us on Facebook and\"}, {\"start\": 626.0, \"end\": 630.0, \"text\": \"follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 631.0, \"end\": 639.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-K-HfBcGPXU": {
    "video_id": "-K-HfBcGPXU",
    "title": "Sign1News 6.3.20",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200603",
    "duration": 828,
    "view_count": 1784,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n\n- Nationwide protests, officers charged for excessive force\n- Update: FBI opens investigation into EMT shot by police\n- Police scanner apps now popular\n- City elects first black mayor, Steve King to lose\n- National Running Day safety tips",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 9.32, \"end\": 10.92, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 10.92, \"end\": 16.0, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 16.0, \"end\": 17.08, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 17.08, \"end\": 20.88, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 26.04, \"end\": 39.28, \"text\": \"Last night was another night of protests, curfews and arrests in cities across the country.\"}, {\"start\": 39.28, \"end\": 48.4, \"text\": \"They are all sparked by last week's killing of George Floyd.\"}, {\"start\": 48.4, \"end\": 56.76, \"text\": \"In Seattle protesters stayed late into the night and brought umbrellas to a protest to\"}, {\"start\": 56.76, \"end\": 63.28, \"text\": \"try to block crowd control chemicals.\"}, {\"start\": 63.28, \"end\": 72.52, \"text\": \"In Los Angeles hundreds were arrested in an act of civil disobedience but it followed\"}, {\"start\": 72.52, \"end\": 76.84, \"text\": \"a day of mostly peaceful marches throughout the city.\"}, {\"start\": 76.84, \"end\": 84.16, \"text\": \"The mayor of Los Angeles met with protesters outside City Hall and acknowledged that work\"}, {\"start\": 84.16, \"end\": 92.6, \"text\": \"needs to be done on race relations but sees hope in the calls for justice.\"}, {\"start\": 92.6, \"end\": 102.96, \"text\": \"In Chicago people gathered peacefully outside Wrigley Field for what a witness called \\\"a\"}, {\"start\": 102.96, \"end\": 109.36, \"text\": \"block party\\\" with protesters and police all coming together.\"}, {\"start\": 109.36, \"end\": 115.04, \"text\": \"In New York thousands marched throughout the streets.\"}, {\"start\": 115.04, \"end\": 117.48, \"text\": \"But not all confrontations ended peacefully.\"}, {\"start\": 117.48, \"end\": 125.36, \"text\": \"There were a number of arrests in New York for violating curfew.\"}, {\"start\": 125.36, \"end\": 134.44, \"text\": \"And in Atlanta the National Guard and police used tear gas to disperse crowds.\"}, {\"start\": 134.44, \"end\": 139.36, \"text\": \"Also in Atlanta we have an update to a story we told you about earlier this week.\"}, {\"start\": 139.36, \"end\": 146.0, \"text\": \"We want to warn you some viewers may find this video disturbing.\"}, {\"start\": 146.0, \"end\": 156.96, \"text\": \"Tuesday arrest warrants were issued for six police officers involved in the arrest of\"}, {\"start\": 156.96, \"end\": 162.56, \"text\": \"two college students during Saturday night's protests.\"}, {\"start\": 162.56, \"end\": 173.84, \"text\": \"The officers were caught on video in downtown Atlanta breaking the windows of the vehicle,\"}, {\"start\": 173.84, \"end\": 180.88, \"text\": \"yanking a woman out of the car and tasing a man.\"}, {\"start\": 180.88, \"end\": 192.56, \"text\": \"Atlanta Mayor Keisha Lance Bottoms terminated two of the six officers Sunday saying excessive\"}, {\"start\": 192.56, \"end\": 197.2, \"text\": \"force was used during the incident.\"}, {\"start\": 197.2, \"end\": 209.68, \"text\": \"The two victims were later identified as Taniyah Pilgrim and Messiah Young.\"}, {\"start\": 209.68, \"end\": 214.08, \"text\": \"Young has a broken arm and wrist.\"}, {\"start\": 214.08, \"end\": 216.4, \"text\": \"He also had to get 24 stitches.\"}, {\"start\": 216.4, \"end\": 223.92, \"text\": \"Tuesday Young the Pilgrim spoke out about their experience at a news conference.\"}, {\"start\": 225.36, \"end\": 237.6, \"text\": \"As protest continue nationwide over the death of George Floyd, many are protesting over\"}, {\"start\": 237.6, \"end\": 243.84, \"text\": \"the death of black EMT Breonna Taylor as well.\"}, {\"start\": 243.84, \"end\": 251.92, \"text\": \"The FBI has opened an investigation into the shooting of Taylor.\"}, {\"start\": 251.92, \"end\": 262.48, \"text\": \"In March Taylor and her boyfriend Kenneth Walker were in her apartment in Louisville,\"}, {\"start\": 262.48, \"end\": 266.64, \"text\": \"Kentucky just before 1 a.m.\"}, {\"start\": 266.64, \"end\": 275.12, \"text\": \"Three officers dressed in plain clothes and not wearing body cameras arrived to execute\"}, {\"start\": 275.12, \"end\": 279.92, \"text\": \"a search warrant in a drug case.\"}, {\"start\": 279.92, \"end\": 289.28, \"text\": \"Taylor and her boyfriend thought someone was breaking in when police kicked down the door.\"}, {\"start\": 289.28, \"end\": 296.24, \"text\": \"Walker grabbed his legal firearm and started shooting, hitting one officer in the leg.\"}, {\"start\": 296.24, \"end\": 304.32, \"text\": \"Officers returned fire and Taylor was shot at least eight times and killed.\"}, {\"start\": 304.32, \"end\": 313.52, \"text\": \"Police say they raided the apartment because another man involved in a drug trafficking\"}, {\"start\": 313.52, \"end\": 322.8, \"text\": \"ring was using Taylor's apartment to ship drugs to avoid detection.\"}, {\"start\": 322.8, \"end\": 328.96, \"text\": \"But according to a lawsuit filed by Taylor's mother in February, the suspect police were\"}, {\"start\": 328.96, \"end\": 336.0, \"text\": \"looking for had already been arrested by other officers executing a warrant at a separate location.\"}, {\"start\": 336.0, \"end\": 344.0, \"text\": \"Her mother argued because of that the search warrant should have been called off.\"}, {\"start\": 344.0, \"end\": 350.16, \"text\": \"Officials also say police found no drugs in the apartment.\"}, {\"start\": 350.16, \"end\": 355.84, \"text\": \"Taylor's boyfriend was arrested and charged with attempted murder of a police officer\"}, {\"start\": 355.84, \"end\": 361.6, \"text\": \"and first-degree assault.\"}, {\"start\": 361.6, \"end\": 364.08, \"text\": \"The charges have since been dropped.\"}, {\"start\": 364.08, \"end\": 371.36, \"text\": \"The Louisville Metro Police Department is now requiring all sworn officers to wear body\"}, {\"start\": 371.36, \"end\": 377.52, \"text\": \"cameras while they serve warrants and in other situations in which they identify themselves\"}, {\"start\": 377.52, \"end\": 380.4, \"text\": \"as police officers.\"}, {\"start\": 380.4, \"end\": 384.96, \"text\": \"None of the officers involved have been arrested.\"}, {\"start\": 389.6, \"end\": 400.8, \"text\": \"Police scanner apps are surging in popularity after days of riots across the United States.\"}, {\"start\": 400.8, \"end\": 412.0, \"text\": \"\\\"50 Radio Police Scanner\\\" is one of the top downloaded apps for iPhones.\"}, {\"start\": 412.0, \"end\": 420.16, \"text\": \"It costs five dollars to download, making it the top paid app in Apple's app store Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 420.16, \"end\": 433.76, \"text\": \"Police scanner apps give real-time information about incidents involving the deployment of\"}, {\"start\": 433.76, \"end\": 442.72, \"text\": \"police, fires, shootings and looting.\"}, {\"start\": 442.72, \"end\": 453.52, \"text\": \"Some scanner apps also let protesters listen to live police radio feeds.\"}, {\"start\": 453.52, \"end\": 459.04, \"text\": \"The developer for 50 Radio Police Scanner says since Sunday the app has had more than\"}, {\"start\": 459.04, \"end\": 466.32, \"text\": \"half a million active users tune in.\"}, {\"start\": 467.28, \"end\": 472.0, \"text\": \"Tuesday several states held primary elections.\"}, {\"start\": 472.0, \"end\": 482.72, \"text\": \"In Ferguson, Missouri, a city with a troubled racial history, voters elected the city's\"}, {\"start\": 482.72, \"end\": 490.08, \"text\": \"first black and female mayor, Ella Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 490.08, \"end\": 501.36, \"text\": \"In 2014 the death of unarmed black teen Michael Brown who was shot by a white police officer\"}, {\"start\": 501.36, \"end\": 503.12, \"text\": \"sparked outrage and protests.\"}, {\"start\": 503.12, \"end\": 509.44, \"text\": \"Jones was elected as Ferguson's first African American city council member the year after\"}, {\"start\": 509.44, \"end\": 512.4, \"text\": \"Brown's death.\"}, {\"start\": 512.4, \"end\": 525.36, \"text\": \"Meanwhile in Iowa CNN projects that long time Congressman Steve King will lose in his Republican\"}, {\"start\": 525.36, \"end\": 529.04, \"text\": \"primary.\"}, {\"start\": 529.04, \"end\": 533.84, \"text\": \"King represented Iowa's fourth congressional district.\"}, {\"start\": 533.84, \"end\": 541.2, \"text\": \"He's gained attention in the past for controversial remarks on race.\"}, {\"start\": 541.2, \"end\": 551.52, \"text\": \"But it wasn't until last year that he was ostracized in Washington and stripped of his\"}, {\"start\": 551.52, \"end\": 559.68, \"text\": \"committee assignments after questioning how \\\"white nationalist, white supremacist, Western\"}, {\"start\": 559.68, \"end\": 562.32, \"text\": \"civilization\\\" became offensive.\"}, {\"start\": 562.32, \"end\": 572.48, \"text\": \"Last June President Trump barred him from Air Force One.\"}, {\"start\": 573.84, \"end\": 588.64, \"text\": \"Grab your running shoes, Wednesday is National Running Day!\"}, {\"start\": 588.64, \"end\": 597.04, \"text\": \"Whether you're an avid runner or a wanna-be runner, today is the day to celebrate\"}, {\"start\": 597.04, \"end\": 601.36, \"text\": \"the love of a good run.\"}, {\"start\": 601.36, \"end\": 612.0, \"text\": \"However officials are encouraging runners not run in groups this year with the coronavirus\"}, {\"start\": 612.0, \"end\": 614.56, \"text\": \"still being very much a threat.\"}, {\"start\": 614.56, \"end\": 626.64, \"text\": \"Participants are encouraged to join in on a game of virtual tag with the #Run1Tag1 challenge,\"}, {\"start\": 626.64, \"end\": 632.96, \"text\": \"which is designed to inspire others to participate by tagging them on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 632.96, \"end\": 639.52, \"text\": \"Here are a few tips on how you can have a safe run.\"}, {\"start\": 639.52, \"end\": 646.32, \"text\": \"First tell someone where you're going and when you'll be back.\"}, {\"start\": 646.32, \"end\": 654.08, \"text\": \"Second make sure you are six feet apart from others in all directions.\"}, {\"start\": 654.08, \"end\": 660.24, \"text\": \"Third plan your running route ahead of time.\"}, {\"start\": 660.32, \"end\": 666.24, \"text\": \"Lastly wash your hands when you get home.\"}, {\"start\": 668.48, \"end\": 670.12, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 670.12, \"end\": 671.0, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 671.0, \"end\": 673.96, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 673.96, \"end\": 683.6, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our app too.\"}, {\"start\": 683.6, \"end\": 689.52, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "DBA7r0XgKUY": {
    "video_id": "DBA7r0XgKUY",
    "title": "Sign1News fan comment: disability emojis (ASL - 3.26.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180327",
    "duration": 81,
    "view_count": 331,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.8, \"end\": 10.04, \"text\": \"A few days ago we told you about Apple's push to add emojis that represent people with disabilities.\"}, {\"start\": 10.04, \"end\": 18.02, \"text\": \"The emojis would include an ear with a hearing aid, a person in a wheelchair, a prosthetic\"}, {\"start\": 18.08, \"end\": 25.34, \"text\": \"arm, a service dog and a person with a cane.\"}, {\"start\": 25.38, \"end\": 29.56, \"text\": \"I think it's a wonderful idea because it involves so much diversity.\"}, {\"start\": 29.64, \"end\": 32.14, \"text\": \"I like it and am really looking forward to it.\"}, {\"start\": 32.14, \"end\": 39.06, \"text\": \"We asked you to submit your thoughts on the disability emojis and here's what you had to say.\"}, {\"start\": 39.06, \"end\": 50.04, \"text\": \"Stella Reid said: \\\"Yes, yes I love the emojis!\"}, {\"start\": 50.04, \"end\": 54.24, \"text\": \"And that will inspire all deaf people in the world.\"}, {\"start\": 54.24, \"end\": 58.14, \"text\": \"There needs to be each country with their own emojis so they can use their own in their\"}, {\"start\": 58.14, \"end\": 59.5, \"text\": \"languages all over the world.\"}, {\"start\": 59.5, \"end\": 61.84, \"text\": \"I love the idea!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 61.84, \"end\": 69.74, \"text\": \"Rick Greco just that one concern.\"}, {\"start\": 69.74, \"end\": 75.92, \"text\": \"He hopes the emojis do not include an image of a cochlear implant.\"}, {\"start\": 75.92, \"end\": 80.58, \"text\": \"Stella and Rick thank you so much for your comments.\"}]"
  },
  "dTftIVNjE8E": {
    "video_id": "dTftIVNjE8E",
    "title": "Sign1News Live 3.1.20",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200301",
    "duration": 764,
    "view_count": 1773,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n\n-U.S. schools prepare for coronavirus impact\n-Joe Biden makes a comeback in South Carolina\n-Purple Communications hosts open house for interpreters in Atlanta\n-McDonald's giving away free McMuffins on Monday March 2\n-Top 5 Stories of the week",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 10.56, \"end\": 11.54, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 11.54, \"end\": 16.08, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 16.08, \"end\": 17.34, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 17.34, \"end\": 20.64, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 27.7, \"end\": 39.78, \"text\": \"With more than 85,000 confirmed cases of coronavirus around the world, preparations are underway\"}, {\"start\": 39.78, \"end\": 44.36, \"text\": \"in school districts across the US to prepare for the impact.\"}, {\"start\": 44.36, \"end\": 59.44, \"text\": \"Many schools already have plans in place for contagions.\"}, {\"start\": 59.44, \"end\": 65.58, \"text\": \"Right now many schools are giving out information to students and parents basically educating\"}, {\"start\": 65.58, \"end\": 72.4, \"text\": \"them about the risk of coronavirus, which still remains low, and also reminding them\"}, {\"start\": 72.4, \"end\": 82.86, \"text\": \"of good hygiene practices by washing hands, covering up a cough and sneeze and staying\"}, {\"start\": 82.86, \"end\": 86.36, \"text\": \"at home if a child is sick.\"}, {\"start\": 86.36, \"end\": 93.82, \"text\": \"However some school districts are planning for the more severe possibility of shutting\"}, {\"start\": 93.82, \"end\": 96.64, \"text\": \"down schools if necessary.\"}, {\"start\": 96.64, \"end\": 105.14, \"text\": \"School officials are pulling together 200,000 laptops, tablets and study packets to give\"}, {\"start\": 105.26, \"end\": 113.16, \"text\": \"to students if they have to learn online from home.\"}, {\"start\": 113.16, \"end\": 119.64, \"text\": \"Experts say colleges and universities could be more vulnerable because they have large\"}, {\"start\": 119.64, \"end\": 126.82, \"text\": \"populations in very close quarters and a lot of students and faculty travel overseas to\"}, {\"start\": 126.82, \"end\": 129.0, \"text\": \"study or teach.\"}, {\"start\": 129.0, \"end\": 136.5, \"text\": \"But many of those study abroad programs have been suspended and some are scaling back or\"}, {\"start\": 136.5, \"end\": 144.28, \"text\": \"canceling large gatherings on campus like sporting events and concerts.\"}, {\"start\": 147.26, \"end\": 157.52, \"text\": \"For weeks Joe Biden has hinged his presidential hopes on South Carolina granting him a come back.\"}, {\"start\": 157.52, \"end\": 160.38, \"text\": \"Last night it looks like he was right.\"}, {\"start\": 160.38, \"end\": 170.84, \"text\": \"The 77-year-old has been running for president off and on for 33 years.\"}, {\"start\": 170.84, \"end\": 176.64, \"text\": \"The victory in South Carolina was his first ever nominating contest win.\"}, {\"start\": 176.64, \"end\": 185.06, \"text\": \"Voters in South Carolina gave Biden a much-needed boost after the former vice president struggled\"}, {\"start\": 185.06, \"end\": 189.04, \"text\": \"in the previous three states.\"}, {\"start\": 189.04, \"end\": 195.24, \"text\": \"But his campaign focused on South Carolina which is the first state with a majority black\"}, {\"start\": 195.24, \"end\": 198.24, \"text\": \"Democratic electorate.\"}, {\"start\": 198.24, \"end\": 211.16, \"text\": \"Now Biden hopes the win will springboard his campaign into Super Tuesday were now a third\"}, {\"start\": 211.16, \"end\": 216.26, \"text\": \"of all pledged delegates are at stake.\"}, {\"start\": 216.26, \"end\": 225.419, \"text\": \"Other candidates are already spending time and money in Super Tuesday states trying to\"}, {\"start\": 225.42, \"end\": 230.84, \"text\": \"prove to voters their campaigns can last.\"}, {\"start\": 230.84, \"end\": 239.16, \"text\": \"Billionaire businessman Tom Steyer is not one of them.\"}, {\"start\": 239.16, \"end\": 245.4, \"text\": \"Steyer announced he is dropping out of the race for president.\"}, {\"start\": 245.4, \"end\": 251.4, \"text\": \"Steyer spent millions of dollars of his own money on his presidential run.\"}, {\"start\": 251.4, \"end\": 255.76, \"text\": \"But it didn't help him gain traction in the Democratic primaries.\"}, {\"start\": 255.76, \"end\": 264.06, \"text\": \"His low finish in South Carolina comes after he invested heavily there.\"}, {\"start\": 264.08, \"end\": 267.12, \"text\": \"So Steyer says it was time to go.\"}, {\"start\": 269.76, \"end\": 280.12, \"text\": \"On Saturday Purple Communications held a small open house at its Atlanta office in search\"}, {\"start\": 280.14, \"end\": 282.84, \"text\": \"of eager video relay service (VRS) interpreters.\"}, {\"start\": 282.84, \"end\": 287.76, \"text\": \"The event offered potential interpreters a chance to see what a VRS center looks like\"}, {\"start\": 287.76, \"end\": 291.36, \"text\": \"and shared the benefits of working with a company like Purple Communications.\"}, {\"start\": 291.36, \"end\": 297.76, \"text\": \"To our surprise, it was also a chance for Sign1News MMJ Martha Anger to reconnect with\"}, {\"start\": 297.76, \"end\": 304.56, \"text\": \"a woman who says she decided to become an interpreter 20 years ago because of the influence\"}, {\"start\": 304.56, \"end\": 308.8, \"text\": \"and impact a 10-year-old Martha had on her.\"}, {\"start\": 308.8, \"end\": 319.2, \"text\": \"But first Purple Communications Atlanta center manager Christopher Patterson explains how\"}, {\"start\": 319.2, \"end\": 326.88, \"text\": \"the company goes the extra mile to make its employees feel right at home.\"}, {\"start\": 329.36, \"end\": 338.64, \"text\": \"This is an example of our interpreter culture here. February for Valentine's Day we asked\"}, {\"start\": 338.64, \"end\": 341.96, \"text\": \"interpreters to put short messages on the wall about the things that inspire them, what\"}, {\"start\": 341.96, \"end\": 351.26, \"text\": \"they are thankful for, why they work here and why they continue to work in VRS.\"}, {\"start\": 351.26, \"end\": 355.08, \"text\": \"And every day they look at the wall, it will continue to uplift them.\"}, {\"start\": 355.08, \"end\": 358.2, \"text\": \"For St. Patrick's Day we will\"}, {\"start\": 358.2, \"end\": 361.14, \"text\": \"put up green clovers with messages.\"}, {\"start\": 361.14, \"end\": 364.52, \"text\": \"We do that every month to help interpreters feel\"}, {\"start\": 364.52, \"end\": 366.4, \"text\": \"inspired and happy.\"}, {\"start\": 381.56, \"end\": 388.9, \"text\": \"The reason we have a massage chair is because interpreters can sometimes feel stress, frustration\"}, {\"start\": 388.9, \"end\": 397.62, \"text\": \"or just need a break to rest. They come into this room to relax and get a chair massage\"}, {\"start\": 397.62, \"end\": 401.02, \"text\": \"to help relieve the stress.\"}, {\"start\": 401.02, \"end\": 409.04, \"text\": \"My first teacher was you. I had not taken any sign language classes before. I was a\"}, {\"start\": 409.04, \"end\": 412.12, \"text\": \"teachers assistant in a public school when I walked into a Deaf classroom. I had no clue\"}, {\"start\": 412.12, \"end\": 419.06, \"text\": \"about sign language. But when I walked into the classroom, I met Deaf children, Deaf teachers\"}, {\"start\": 419.06, \"end\": 422.4, \"text\": \"and other hearing interpreters. I learned sign language quickly and became passionate\"}, {\"start\": 422.4, \"end\": 425.6, \"text\": \"about it. I met you!\"}, {\"start\": 434.22, \"end\": 442.24, \"text\": \"McDonald's is offering free Egg McMuffin's Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 442.26, \"end\": 450.34, \"text\": \"McDonald's is calling March 2 \\\"National Egg McMuffin Day.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 450.34, \"end\": 455.16, \"text\": \"The sandwiches have been around since 1971.\"}, {\"start\": 455.16, \"end\": 465.16, \"text\": \"So the chain says it's celebrating 50 years - a year early.\"}, {\"start\": 465.16, \"end\": 474.6, \"text\": \"Customers can get the free sandwiches between 6 and 10:30 in the morning.\"}, {\"start\": 474.6, \"end\": 480.0, \"text\": \"You'll need the McDonald's app to do so.\"}, {\"start\": 480.009, \"end\": 488.319, \"text\": \"Oh by the way March 2 is also the same day Wendy's is launching its breakfast menu.\"}, {\"start\": 488.319, \"end\": 500.06, \"text\": \"Wendy's new breakfast lineup includes the breakfast baconator, frosty-ccino and honey\"}, {\"start\": 500.06, \"end\": 502.54, \"text\": \"butter chicken biscuit.\"}, {\"start\": 507.37, \"end\": 514.44, \"text\": \"Here's a quick recap of the top five Sign1News stories of the week.\"}, {\"start\": 514.44, \"end\": 517.46, \"text\": \"Concerns about the spread of the coronavirus dominated the headlines and caused ripple\"}, {\"start\": 517.46, \"end\": 519.1, \"text\": \"effects all over the globe.\"}, {\"start\": 519.1, \"end\": 530.46, \"text\": \"The stock market dipped to a historic low, schools in Asia are closing as a precaution,\"}, {\"start\": 530.46, \"end\": 537.7, \"text\": \"TV shows and concerts are being canceled and the US is dealing with its first recorded\"}, {\"start\": 537.7, \"end\": 543.12, \"text\": \"coronavirus death believed to be associated with \\\"community spread,\\\" which means person\"}, {\"start\": 543.12, \"end\": 549.84, \"text\": \"to person with no ties to traveling or contact with another coronavirus patient.\"}, {\"start\": 549.84, \"end\": 562.87, \"text\": \"Deaf rapper Sean Forbes shot to the top of iTunes and Amazon's digital music charts with\"}, {\"start\": 562.87, \"end\": 572.88, \"text\": \"the release of his new album \\\"Little Victories\\\" thanks to a national grassroots movement in\"}, {\"start\": 572.92, \"end\": 574.42, \"text\": \"the Deaf community.\"}, {\"start\": 574.42, \"end\": 580.9, \"text\": \"If he continues to climb in the charts, Forbes will become the first Deaf artist to land\"}, {\"start\": 580.96, \"end\": 585.26, \"text\": \"on the Billboard 200 chart.\"}, {\"start\": 585.26, \"end\": 593.4, \"text\": \"The world mourned the death of mathematician Katherine Johnson.\"}, {\"start\": 593.4, \"end\": 603.36, \"text\": \"Her pioneering work was part of NASA's \\\"computer pool\\\" in the 1960s that helped power the agency's\"}, {\"start\": 603.36, \"end\": 613.7, \"text\": \"first successful space missions and inspired the 2017 film \\\"Hidden Figures.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 613.7, \"end\": 618.3, \"text\": \"Johnson died at 101 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 618.3, \"end\": 624.06, \"text\": \"The Los Angeles County Sheriff's Department is looking into reports that some of its deputies\"}, {\"start\": 624.06, \"end\": 630.64, \"text\": \"shared graphic photos of the helicopter crash that killed Kobe Bryant and eight others,\"}, {\"start\": 630.64, \"end\": 636.76, \"text\": \"photos that may have included images of the victims' bodies.\"}, {\"start\": 636.76, \"end\": 649.94, \"text\": \"Today Bryant's widow Vanessa is demanding that those responsible for the alleged allegations\"}, {\"start\": 649.94, \"end\": 658.56, \"text\": \"face the harshest possible discipline and their identities be brought to light.\"}, {\"start\": 658.56, \"end\": 667.02, \"text\": \"And the story of a little boy who dropped his puppy off at a Mexican animal rescue shelter\"}, {\"start\": 667.02, \"end\": 671.68, \"text\": \"to protect it from being abused by his father touched the hearts of people all over the country.\"}, {\"start\": 671.68, \"end\": 685.3, \"text\": \"The boy left a note explaining the abuse the dog suffered and a toy so the dog wouldn't\"}, {\"start\": 685.3, \"end\": 686.36, \"text\": \"forget it.\"}, {\"start\": 686.36, \"end\": 694.6, \"text\": \"The dog is still getting medical attention and will be available for adoption soon.\"}, {\"start\": 697.48, \"end\": 699.49, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 699.49, \"end\": 700.44, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 700.44, \"end\": 703.06, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 703.06, \"end\": 712.06, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our app too.\"}, {\"start\": 712.1, \"end\": 716.08, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "bt6EbW45g78": {
    "video_id": "bt6EbW45g78",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.1.17- News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171102",
    "duration": 511,
    "view_count": 805,
    "description": "November 1, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-NYC TERROR ATTACK SUSPECT\n-NYC TERROR ATTACK INVESTIGATION\n-TRUMP HOLDS CABINET MEETING\n-OBAMACARE 2018 ENROLLMENT OPENS TODAY \n-WENDY WILLIAMS FAINTS ON LIVE TV  \n-DAD GIVES NEWBORN PEP TALK  \n-SONY BRINGS BACK \"AIBO\"\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET U",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I'm Candace Jones\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"and here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.0, \"end\": 23.0, \"text\": \"Investigators in New York are still gathering information about Sayfullo Saipov.\"}, {\"start\": 24.0, \"end\": 30.0, \"text\": \"Police say he is responsible for Tuesday's terror attack.\"}, {\"start\": 30.0, \"end\": 35.0, \"text\": \"Yesterday around 3:00 p.m. he drove a rented\"}, {\"start\": 35.0, \"end\": 40.0, \"text\": \"truck down a crowded bike path\"}, {\"start\": 40.0, \"end\": 45.0, \"text\": \"and killed eight people. More than a dozen were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 51.0, \"text\": \"Saipov is 29 years old originally from\"}, {\"start\": 51.0, \"end\": 56.0, \"text\": \"Uzbekistan but he moved to the U.S. in\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 61.0, \"text\": \"2010. Officials at Uber say he started\"}, {\"start\": 61.0, \"end\": 65.0, \"text\": \"working at the company earlier this year.\"}, {\"start\": 65.0, \"end\": 72.0, \"text\": \"He passed a background check but is now banned from the business.\"}, {\"start\": 72.0, \"end\": 76.0, \"text\": \"And take a look at this.\"}, {\"start\": 76.0, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"This picture was taken just moments after a police officer\"}, {\"start\": 81.0, \"end\": 86.0, \"text\": \"shot Saipov. It shows Saipov\"}, {\"start\": 86.0, \"end\": 90.0, \"text\": \"on the ground in the fetal position surrounded by two police officers.\"}, {\"start\": 93.0, \"end\": 98.0, \"text\": \"New York officials say the investigation into yesterday's\"}, {\"start\": 98.0, \"end\": 104.0, \"text\": \"terror attack is just getting started.\"}, {\"start\": 104.0, \"end\": 109.0, \"text\": \"The FBI, NYPD and other members\"}, {\"start\": 109.0, \"end\": 114.0, \"text\": \"of the Joint Terrorism Task Force say they are working\"}, {\"start\": 114.0, \"end\": 119.0, \"text\": \"hard to get to the bottom of exactly what happened\"}, {\"start\": 119.0, \"end\": 125.0, \"text\": \"and more importantly why it happened.\"}, {\"start\": 125.0, \"end\": 129.0, \"text\": \"They have learned that\"}, {\"start\": 130.0, \"end\": 134.0, \"text\": \"the attacker had been\"}, {\"start\": 135.0, \"end\": 143.0, \"text\": \"planning this attack for weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 145.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"And that he did it in the name of ISIS.\"}, {\"start\": 149.0, \"end\": 155.0, \"text\": \"They also found handwritten notes near the scene saying\"}, {\"start\": 155.0, \"end\": 162.0, \"text\": \"ISIS will endure forever.\"}, {\"start\": 165.0, \"end\": 170.0, \"text\": \"President Trump held a cabinet meeting\"}, {\"start\": 171.0, \"end\": 176.0, \"text\": \"at the White House today and he made a couple of eyebrow\"}, {\"start\": 176.0, \"end\": 181.0, \"text\": \"raising comments.\"}, {\"start\": 181.0, \"end\": 187.0, \"text\": \"First he called the U.S. justice system a joke.\"}, {\"start\": 187.0, \"end\": 192.0, \"text\": \"He insinuated that terror attacks happen in the\"}, {\"start\": 192.0, \"end\": 199.0, \"text\": \"United States because of a lax legal system.\"}, {\"start\": 199.0, \"end\": 203.0, \"text\": \"He also called for a\"}, {\"start\": 204.0, \"end\": 209.0, \"text\": \"speedier legal process\"}, {\"start\": 209.0, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"and harsher punishments.\"}, {\"start\": 217.0, \"end\": 221.0, \"text\": \"He also said he wants to terminate the Diversity\"}, {\"start\": 221.0, \"end\": 227.0, \"text\": \"Visa Lottery program.\"}, {\"start\": 227.0, \"end\": 232.0, \"text\": \"The program distributes about 50,000 visas\"}, {\"start\": 232.0, \"end\": 237.0, \"text\": \"to countries where there is a low\"}, {\"start\": 237.0, \"end\": 242.0, \"text\": \"rate of U.S. immigration. He said\"}, {\"start\": 242.0, \"end\": 246.0, \"text\": \"he would consider sending the New York City attack\"}, {\"start\": 247.0, \"end\": 254.0, \"text\": \"suspect to the controversial prison at Guantanamo Bay.\"}, {\"start\": 257.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"Open enrollment for Obamacare starts\"}, {\"start\": 261.0, \"end\": 265.0, \"text\": \"today. According to a recent report from the\"}, {\"start\": 265.0, \"end\": 270.0, \"text\": \"Department of Health and Human Services 80 percent of\"}, {\"start\": 270.0, \"end\": 274.0, \"text\": \"Americans can get a 2018 plan for less\"}, {\"start\": 274.0, \"end\": 279.0, \"text\": \"than $75 per month. Last year\"}, {\"start\": 279.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"71 percent of enrollees could find that same rate.\"}, {\"start\": 288.0, \"end\": 292.0, \"text\": \"For most U.S states open enrollment\"}, {\"start\": 292.0, \"end\": 298.0, \"text\": \"starts today and runs through December 15.\"}, {\"start\": 302.024, \"end\": 305.024, \"text\": \"There was a scary moment on TV Tuesday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 305.1, \"end\": 310.0, \"text\": \"Talk show host Wendy Williams\"}, {\"start\": 310.0, \"end\": 316.0, \"text\": \"passed out on live TV.\"}, {\"start\": 318.0, \"end\": 321.0, \"text\": \"Williams was dressed in a\"}, {\"start\": 321.0, \"end\": 326.0, \"text\": \"Statue of Liberty costume.\"}, {\"start\": 326.0, \"end\": 331.0, \"text\": \"When she started to introduce a guest\"}, {\"start\": 331.0, \"end\": 336.0, \"text\": \"her speech became garbled and she fainted.\"}, {\"start\": 336.0, \"end\": 339.0, \"text\": \"Some people thought it was a stunt\"}, {\"start\": 339.0, \"end\": 344.0, \"text\": \"but Williams later told audience members\"}, {\"start\": 345.0, \"end\": 351.0, \"text\": \"she overheated in her costume.\"}, {\"start\": 352.0, \"end\": 355.0, \"text\": \"She was examined by a doctor\"}, {\"start\": 355.0, \"end\": 358.0, \"text\": \"and went on to finish the show.\"}, {\"start\": 361.0, \"end\": 367.0, \"text\": \"This video has gone viral\"}, {\"start\": 367.0, \"end\": 372.0, \"text\": \"on social media. Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 372.0, \"end\": 380.0, \"text\": \"It shows first-time father Antwon comforting his newborn\"}, {\"start\": 381.0, \"end\": 385.0, \"text\": \"son Debias King Lee through his first\"}, {\"start\": 385.024, \"end\": 392.024, \"text\": \"immunization shots.\"}, {\"start\": 392.1, \"end\": 398.1, \"text\": \"As the nurse delivered multiple shots the father talks his son through the pain.\"}, {\"start\": 398.124, \"end\": 400.924, \"text\": \"The baby cried the entire time.\"}, {\"start\": 402.0, \"end\": 406.0, \"text\": \"But when the shots were over dad he was there to comfort his son.\"}, {\"start\": 406.0, \"end\": 413.0, \"text\": \"And within minutes the baby stopped crying.\"}, {\"start\": 413.0, \"end\": 417.0, \"text\": \"That precious moment between father and son has been viewed more than\"}, {\"start\": 417.0, \"end\": 425.0, \"text\": \"13 million times on Facebook.\"}, {\"start\": 428.0, \"end\": 434.0, \"text\": \"Sony is bringing back Aibo -- its famous robotic dog.\"}, {\"start\": 435.0, \"end\": 440.0, \"text\": \"The dog can respond to voice commands. It can bark, sit, wag its tail and\"}, {\"start\": 440.0, \"end\": 446.0, \"text\": \"connect to mobile networks.\"}, {\"start\": 446.0, \"end\": 448.0, \"text\": \"But it won't bite.\"}, {\"start\": 449.0, \"end\": 455.0, \"text\": \"The eyes are small screens that show an array of facial expressions.\"}, {\"start\": 455.0, \"end\": 460.0, \"text\": \"And the dog is expected to be more intelligent\"}, {\"start\": 460.0, \"end\": 465.0, \"text\": \"than previous models.\"}, {\"start\": 466.0, \"end\": 470.0, \"text\": \"Pre-orders for Aibo began today\"}, {\"start\": 470.0, \"end\": 475.0, \"text\": \"but only for Japan.\"}, {\"start\": 476.0, \"end\": 480.0, \"text\": \"Everyone else can start ordering in January.\"}, {\"start\": 480.0, \"end\": 484.0, \"text\": \"The cost is a little over $1700.\"}, {\"start\": 487.0, \"end\": 490.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 490.024, \"end\": 497.024, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 497.1, \"end\": 502.1, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "CePMsA2CxM4": {
    "video_id": "CePMsA2CxM4",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.23.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171024",
    "duration": 575,
    "view_count": 245,
    "description": "October 23, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-FEUD ESCALATES BETWEEN TRUMP AND WILSON\n-WIDOW OF SLAIN U.S. SOLDIER SPEAKS OUT\n-10 MORE SUSPECTS IDENTIFIED FROM \"UNITE THE RIGHT\" RALLY\n-MAN STALKS KIDS, WRITES LETTER TO PARENTS \n-JUSTIN TIMBERLAKE TO HEADLINE SUPERBOWL HALFTIME\n-TARGET OFFERING FREE SHIPPING FOR HOLIDAYS \n-PIGLET RESCUED BY STATE PATROL\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliv",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.0, \"end\": 15.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.0, \"end\": 22.0, \"text\": \"It's been nearly a week and President Trump and Congresswoman\"}, {\"start\": 22.0, \"end\": 26.0, \"text\": \"Frederica Wilson continue to\"}, {\"start\": 26.0, \"end\": 32.0, \"text\": \"argue back and forth.\"}, {\"start\": 32.0, \"end\": 36.0, \"text\": \"The argument is over what Trump\"}, {\"start\": 36.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"said to the widow of a soldier killed\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 47.0, \"text\": \"in the Niger ambush. According\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"to Wilson, Trump told the wife of\"}, {\"start\": 54.0, \"end\": 59.0, \"text\": \"Sergeant La David Johnson\"}, {\"start\": 59.0, \"end\": 63.0, \"text\": \"that he quote\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 68.0, \"text\": \"\\\"knew what he signed up for. But I guess it still hurts.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 68.0, \"end\": 72.0, \"text\": \"Wilson also said Trump\"}, {\"start\": 73.0, \"end\": 77.0, \"text\": \"couldn't even remember the soldier's name and the\"}, {\"start\": 77.0, \"end\": 80.0, \"text\": \"conversation left the soldier's wife in tears.\"}, {\"start\": 80.0, \"end\": 88.0, \"text\": \"Trump says that never happened and\"}, {\"start\": 88.0, \"end\": 93.0, \"text\": \"he has proof but he doesn't say what the proof is.\"}, {\"start\": 94.001, \"end\": 95.901, \"text\": \"Trump says the conversation\"}, {\"start\": 96.0, \"end\": 100.0, \"text\": \"was nice and completely respectful.\"}, {\"start\": 100.0, \"end\": 103.0, \"text\": \"He also said that he said Sergeant Johnson's name\"}, {\"start\": 104.0, \"end\": 111.0, \"text\": \"from the beginning without hesitation.\"}, {\"start\": 115.0, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"Today the widow of Sergeant La David Johnson\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 125.0, \"text\": \"spoke for the first time to set the record straight\"}, {\"start\": 125.0, \"end\": 128.0, \"text\": \"about the phone call from the president.\"}, {\"start\": 128.0, \"end\": 133.0, \"text\": \"Myeshia Johnson\"}, {\"start\": 133.0, \"end\": 139.0, \"text\": \"was interviewed on ABC network's Good Morning America.\"}, {\"start\": 139.0, \"end\": 144.0, \"text\": \"She said everything Congresswoman Wilson said about\"}, {\"start\": 144.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"what Trump said is correct. And that\"}, {\"start\": 149.0, \"end\": 154.0, \"text\": \"she was angered by the tone of the president's voice.\"}, {\"start\": 155.0, \"end\": 160.0, \"text\": \"But she says that phone conversation is not her biggest concern right now.\"}, {\"start\": 161.0, \"end\": 165.0, \"text\": \"It's been three weeks since her husband was killed in Niger\"}, {\"start\": 166.0, \"end\": 169.0, \"text\": \"and Johnson says she still doesn't know how he died,\"}, {\"start\": 169.0, \"end\": 176.0, \"text\": \"where he got killed and why it took 48 hours to find his dead body.\"}, {\"start\": 177.0, \"end\": 182.0, \"text\": \"The Pentagon and the FBI are investigating\"}, {\"start\": 183.0, \"end\": 188.0, \"text\": \"the October 4th attack\"}, {\"start\": 189.0, \"end\": 193.0, \"text\": \"to get answers to those questions.\"}, {\"start\": 196.0, \"end\": 199.0, \"text\": \"Take a close look at these pictures.\"}, {\"start\": 201.0, \"end\": 205.0, \"text\": \"Police in Charlottesville Virginia\"}, {\"start\": 206.0, \"end\": 211.0, \"text\": \"need your help in identifying several suspects.\"}, {\"start\": 211.0, \"end\": 215.0, \"text\": \"These people were at the\"}, {\"start\": 215.0, \"end\": 222.0, \"text\": \"Unite the Right rally in August.\"}, {\"start\": 223.0, \"end\": 228.0, \"text\": \"This is the rally where a woman was\"}, {\"start\": 228.0, \"end\": 233.0, \"text\": \"killed when a man drove his car into\"}, {\"start\": 233.0, \"end\": 236.0, \"text\": \"a group of counter-protesters.\"}, {\"start\": 236.0, \"end\": 243.0, \"text\": \"Police say a different assault took place during the same rally\"}, {\"start\": 243.0, \"end\": 246.0, \"text\": \"and they released the 10 photos of the suspects\"}, {\"start\": 246.0, \"end\": 252.0, \"text\": \"they would like to talk to.\"}, {\"start\": 252.0, \"end\": 257.0, \"text\": \"Again take a good look.\"}, {\"start\": 257.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"If you recognize anyone in these pictures you are asked to\"}, {\"start\": 262.0, \"end\": 266.0, \"text\": \"contact the Charlottesville Police Department.\"}, {\"start\": 270.0, \"end\": 275.0, \"text\": \"New York police also needs your help identifying this\"}, {\"start\": 275.0, \"end\": 280.0, \"text\": \"man. He is suspected of\"}, {\"start\": 280.0, \"end\": 284.0, \"text\": \"stalking two children.\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 289.0, \"text\": \"This video was captured outside the children's home. The man\"}, {\"start\": 289.0, \"end\": 294.0, \"text\": \"can be seen staring into the house. An 8 year old\"}, {\"start\": 294.0, \"end\": 298.0, \"text\": \"girl who lives in the house says last week\"}, {\"start\": 299.0, \"end\": 306.0, \"text\": \"the man followed her to a school bus stop.\"}, {\"start\": 306.0, \"end\": 311.0, \"text\": \"Later that day the man flagged\"}, {\"start\": 311.0, \"end\": 316.0, \"text\": \"down another school bus that her 12 year old brother was riding.\"}, {\"start\": 317.0, \"end\": 321.0, \"text\": \"The man told the driver that he was there\"}, {\"start\": 323.0, \"end\": 328.0, \"text\": \"to pick the boy up. The bus driver threatened to\"}, {\"start\": 328.0, \"end\": 332.0, \"text\": \"call the police and the man ran.\"}, {\"start\": 333.0, \"end\": 337.0, \"text\": \"The girl saw the man again later that evening\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 342.0, \"text\": \"in front of her house taking pictures.\"}, {\"start\": 343.0, \"end\": 347.0, \"text\": \"The man asked the girl what bedroom she sleeps in\"}, {\"start\": 348.0, \"end\": 352.0, \"text\": \"and who else lives in the house. He came back the\"}, {\"start\": 352.0, \"end\": 357.0, \"text\": \"following day and asked the boy similar\"}, {\"start\": 357.0, \"end\": 361.0, \"text\": \"questions. When the parents came\"}, {\"start\": 362.0, \"end\": 369.0, \"text\": \"home they found a note in the mailbox. The note said\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 375.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Watch out.  I'm watching you. Your daughter is cute.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 380.0, \"end\": 383.0, \"text\": \"Multiple Grammy winning artist\"}, {\"start\": 384.0, \"end\": 389.0, \"text\": \"Justin Timberlake is headlining the\"}, {\"start\": 389.0, \"end\": 394.0, \"text\": \"Super Bowl Pepsi halftime show. He made the announcement on\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"Twitter last night in a comedy sketch with The Tonight Show host\"}, {\"start\": 399.0, \"end\": 403.0, \"text\": \"Jimmy Fallon. Pepsi and the NFL\"}, {\"start\": 403.024, \"end\": 408.099, \"text\": \"confirmed the news.\"}, {\"start\": 408.1, \"end\": 412.1, \"text\": \"This is the first time since 2004 Timberlake\"}, {\"start\": 412.1, \"end\": 417.1, \"text\": \"has headlined the show after a\"}, {\"start\": 418.0, \"end\": 426.0, \"text\": \"wardrobe malfunction on stage\"}, {\"start\": 429.0, \"end\": 434.0, \"text\": \"with Janet Jackson. Super Bowl 52 will be held in Minneapolis\"}, {\"start\": 435.0, \"end\": 439.0, \"text\": \"on February 4th 2018.\"}, {\"start\": 441.0, \"end\": 446.0, \"text\": \"If you don't want to deal with the holiday shopping crowd this year\"}, {\"start\": 446.0, \"end\": 450.0, \"text\": \"Target is offering free shipping on merchandise purchased\"}, {\"start\": 450.0, \"end\": 456.0, \"text\": \"on its Web site. The offer starts next month.\"}, {\"start\": 456.0, \"end\": 460.0, \"text\": \"Target is also debuting more than 17 hundred\"}, {\"start\": 460.0, \"end\": 467.0, \"text\": \"new products to tempt customers.\"}, {\"start\": 467.0, \"end\": 472.0, \"text\": \"Most of the products will cost less than $15.\"}, {\"start\": 472.0, \"end\": 478.0, \"text\": \"Target is also offering stocking stuffers that cost just one dollar.\"}, {\"start\": 478.0, \"end\": 482.0, \"text\": \"Also starting next month shoppers that have Target store\"}, {\"start\": 482.0, \"end\": 487.0, \"text\": \"credit cards will be able to pay\"}, {\"start\": 487.0, \"end\": 492.0, \"text\": \"for purchases by scanning their phones.\"}, {\"start\": 498.0, \"end\": 501.0, \"text\": \"Earlier this month police\"}, {\"start\": 501.0, \"end\": 505.0, \"text\": \"in Nebraska rescued this little piglet.\"}, {\"start\": 506.0, \"end\": 512.0, \"text\": \"A state patrol officer saw the piglet running free in the middle of the highway.\"}, {\"start\": 512.0, \"end\": 518.0, \"text\": \"The trooper managed to scoop the piglet up and\"}, {\"start\": 518.0, \"end\": 523.0, \"text\": \"put him in his patrol car. The piglet was then taken to the Humane Society to\"}, {\"start\": 523.0, \"end\": 525.0, \"text\": \"to be adopted.\"}, {\"start\": 526.0, \"end\": 530.0, \"text\": \"The Humane Society decided\"}, {\"start\": 530.0, \"end\": 536.0, \"text\": \"to name the piglet Wilbur\"}, {\"start\": 536.0, \"end\": 540.0, \"text\": \"in honor of the famous piglet from\"}, {\"start\": 540.0, \"end\": 548.0, \"text\": \"the book Charlotte's Web.\"}, {\"start\": 550.01, \"end\": 553.01, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories today.  I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 553.2, \"end\": 559.2, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sgn1News. Remember to like us on Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 559.2, \"end\": 566.2, \"text\": \"and follow us on Twitter. Sign 1 news. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "ZJtQuntEBMU": {
    "video_id": "ZJtQuntEBMU",
    "title": "Sign1News Live 3.6.20",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200306",
    "duration": 697,
    "view_count": 984,
    "description": "",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 9.26, \"end\": 11.46, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 11.46, \"end\": 15.64, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News Live.\"}, {\"start\": 15.64, \"end\": 18.0, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 18.0, \"end\": 22.26, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 26.44, \"end\": 31.9, \"text\": \"Here's a look at the impact coronavirus concerns are having in schools and businesses across\"}, {\"start\": 31.9, \"end\": 34.06, \"text\": \"the country.\"}, {\"start\": 38.42, \"end\": 47.94, \"text\": \"57 schools have been shut down temporarily and students are being taught online.\"}, {\"start\": 47.94, \"end\": 58.58, \"text\": \"Amazon, Facebook, Google and Microsoft are all encouraging people in the Seattle area\"}, {\"start\": 58.58, \"end\": 61.64, \"text\": \"to work from home.\"}, {\"start\": 61.64, \"end\": 75.14, \"text\": \"And airline companies like United and JetBlue are making cuts to prepare for the 113-billion\"}, {\"start\": 75.14, \"end\": 87.38, \"text\": \"dollars global airlines stand to lose if the coronavirus continues to spread.\"}, {\"start\": 87.38, \"end\": 94.92, \"text\": \"Schools here in Georgia and across the country received letters similar to this one from\"}, {\"start\": 94.92, \"end\": 98.56, \"text\": \"the Department of Education.\"}, {\"start\": 98.56, \"end\": 105.74, \"text\": \"The letter was handed out to parents informing them of the steps being taken to ensure the\"}, {\"start\": 105.74, \"end\": 112.84, \"text\": \"safety of their children and it stresses the importance of practicing simple hygiene like\"}, {\"start\": 112.84, \"end\": 121.0, \"text\": \"washing hands frequently and keeping a child at home if he or she is ill.\"}, {\"start\": 121.0, \"end\": 126.63, \"text\": \"However at a Senate appropriations meeting in Washington, D.C. on Thursday education\"}, {\"start\": 126.63, \"end\": 136.18, \"text\": \"Secretary Betsy DeVos had to address another issue that has arisen in schools as a result\"}, {\"start\": 136.18, \"end\": 145.88, \"text\": \"of the coronavirus: bullying of students based on ethnicity or race.\"}, {\"start\": 145.88, \"end\": 152.39, \"text\": \"The civil rights arm of the Department of Education sent a letter to educators urging\"}, {\"start\": 152.39, \"end\": 161.42, \"text\": \"them to pay careful attention to and address any harassment or unfair treatment of students\"}, {\"start\": 161.42, \"end\": 169.84, \"text\": \"who are perceived to be Chinese-American or of Asian descent.\"}, {\"start\": 169.84, \"end\": 178.66, \"text\": \"Health experts say Wuhan, China is the epicenter of the coronavirus.\"}, {\"start\": 178.66, \"end\": 191.06, \"text\": \"The letter said, in part, \\\"some individuals may regrettably turn toward racial or ethnic\"}, {\"start\": 191.06, \"end\": 200.34, \"text\": \"stereotyping which exacerbates hatred and harms students. These incidents can create\"}, {\"start\": 200.34, \"end\": 209.32, \"text\": \"a climate of misunderstanding and fear. This hurts us all.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 212.46, \"end\": 218.24, \"text\": \"The search for two missing Idaho children continues.\"}, {\"start\": 218.24, \"end\": 225.0, \"text\": \"And the FBI is asking the public for some very specific help in the search.\"}, {\"start\": 225.0, \"end\": 234.86, \"text\": \"The request comes as the mother of the children, 48-year-old Lori Vallow, who is in jail, refuses\"}, {\"start\": 234.86, \"end\": 238.18, \"text\": \"to help with the investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 238.2, \"end\": 254.22, \"text\": \"Seven-year-old JJ Vallow and his sister 17-year-old Tylee Ryan were last seen in September.\"}, {\"start\": 254.24, \"end\": 263.1, \"text\": \"The FBI's Salt Lake city field office is asking people to submit images or video from Yellowstone\"}, {\"start\": 263.1, \"end\": 277.32, \"text\": \"National Park that may show the two missing kids. Specifically from September 8th, 2019.\"}, {\"start\": 277.34, \"end\": 286.2, \"text\": \"Authorities say their mother went to Yellowstone with the children on that day.\"}, {\"start\": 286.2, \"end\": 297.36, \"text\": \"Police say Vallow and her husband fled Idaho when investigators started looking\"}, {\"start\": 297.36, \"end\": 299.84, \"text\": \"into their disappearance.\"}, {\"start\": 299.84, \"end\": 308.76, \"text\": \"Last month Vallow was arrested and faces multiple charges, including two felony counts of desertion\"}, {\"start\": 308.76, \"end\": 311.58, \"text\": \"and non-support of children.\"}, {\"start\": 311.58, \"end\": 320.76, \"text\": \"According to court documents, Vallow also asked people to lie to the authorities during\"}, {\"start\": 320.76, \"end\": 324.82, \"text\": \"the investigation into the disappearances.\"}, {\"start\": 324.82, \"end\": 332.8, \"text\": \"On Thursday (Yesterday) she arrived in Idaho after being extradited from Hawaii.\"}, {\"start\": 332.8, \"end\": 339.78, \"text\": \"Vallow makes a court appearance Friday (Today).\"}, {\"start\": 339.78, \"end\": 344.58, \"text\": \"Bail is set at five-million dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 344.58, \"end\": 351.8, \"text\": \"Vallow's husband, Chad Daybell, currently isn't facing any charges.\"}, {\"start\": 355.7, \"end\": 366.98, \"text\": \"Attorney General William Barr may have to answer for his handling of the Mueller report\"}, {\"start\": 366.98, \"end\": 369.18, \"text\": \"released last spring.\"}, {\"start\": 369.18, \"end\": 380.56, \"text\": \"The report covers findings and conclusions from former special counsel Robert Mueller's\"}, {\"start\": 380.56, \"end\": 387.68, \"text\": \"investigation into Russian interference in the 2016 election.\"}, {\"start\": 387.68, \"end\": 399.1, \"text\": \"Federal judge Reggie Walton criticized Barr's rollout of the heavily redacted report and\"}, {\"start\": 399.1, \"end\": 410.12, \"text\": \"asked if Barr timed and framed the release to help protect President Trump's political interests.\"}, {\"start\": 410.12, \"end\": 416.24, \"text\": \"Barr has been criticized for months over the report.\"}, {\"start\": 416.24, \"end\": 432.0, \"text\": \"Critics say he deliberately mischaracterized its contents before it was made public.\"}, {\"start\": 432.0, \"end\": 445.42, \"text\": \"Walton says he will review the report to make sure the Justice Department didn't over-redact\"}, {\"start\": 445.42, \"end\": 447.38, \"text\": \"if before it was released.\"}, {\"start\": 447.38, \"end\": 457.3, \"text\": \"If he finds it did, he could order the department to make more of the report available.\"}, {\"start\": 460.92, \"end\": 471.08, \"text\": \"NASA's next Mars rover has a new name...Perseverance.\"}, {\"start\": 471.08, \"end\": 477.98, \"text\": \"That's thanks to Virgina 7th grader Alexander Mather.\"}, {\"start\": 477.98, \"end\": 489.0, \"text\": \"The name came as a result of a contest NASA held that drew more than 28-thousand entries.\"}, {\"start\": 489.0, \"end\": 497.64, \"text\": \"Students representing every state, ranging in age from kindergarten to twelfth grade,\"}, {\"start\": 497.64, \"end\": 500.24, \"text\": \"submitted their favorite names.\"}, {\"start\": 500.24, \"end\": 508.5, \"text\": \"Alexander not only got to name the rover, but he will also receive an invitation to\"}, {\"start\": 508.5, \"end\": 518.62, \"text\": \"travel with his family to Cape Canaveral, a cape and city in Brevard County, Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 518.62, \"end\": 528.46, \"text\": \"There, he will witness the rover being launched into space to begin its mission this summer.\"}, {\"start\": 528.46, \"end\": 537.04, \"text\": \"Alexander explained he came up with the name \\\"Perseverance\\\" because it means humans won't\"}, {\"start\": 537.08, \"end\": 545.52, \"text\": \"give up on the \\\"inevitable setbacks\\\" that we face on the way to Mars.\"}, {\"start\": 547.74, \"end\": 553.88, \"text\": \"Today (Friday) starts the National Day of Unplugging.\"}, {\"start\": 553.88, \"end\": 563.34, \"text\": \"The 24-hour event starts sundown Friday and ends sundown Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 563.34, \"end\": 573.04, \"text\": \"It's a chance to remember what life was like before cell phones and tablets.\"}, {\"start\": 573.04, \"end\": 580.34, \"text\": \"It's part of a project that tries to get people to enjoy the real world.\"}, {\"start\": 580.34, \"end\": 594.68, \"text\": \"Organizers draw upon the Jewish belief in the Sabbath day of rest...in this case, from technology.\"}, {\"start\": 594.68, \"end\": 599.92, \"text\": \"Participants can take a pledge to unplug on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 599.92, \"end\": 610.54, \"text\": \"Or, they can skip the apps and just pick up a book, go for walk, or interact with people in person.\"}, {\"start\": 610.54, \"end\": 615.9, \"text\": \"Do you plan to participate in the event? Let us know in the comments!\"}, {\"start\": 617.94, \"end\": 620.22, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 620.22, \"end\": 621.68, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 621.68, \"end\": 624.64, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News Live.\"}, {\"start\": 624.64, \"end\": 633.78, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download the app too.\"}, {\"start\": 633.78, \"end\": 638.58, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "RKZl8E2Dykk": {
    "video_id": "RKZl8E2Dykk",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.9.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180210",
    "duration": 488,
    "view_count": 1582,
    "description": "2.9.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-White House Aide Scandal: Who knew what when?\n-Government shutdown ends\n-Teens running for governor thanks to loophole\n-Drowsy driving is deadly\n-World’s first zero gravity dance party\n-High school sets record for the most twins\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.54, \"end\": 8.94, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.94, \"end\": 10.76, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.76, \"end\": 12.44, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.44, \"end\": 15.24, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.68, \"end\": 24.68, \"text\": \"The resignation of White House staff secretary Rob Porter after accusations that he abused\"}, {\"start\": 24.68, \"end\": 33.94, \"text\": \"both of his ex-wives has raised lots of questions about who knew what and when, and why no one\"}, {\"start\": 33.94, \"end\": 42.54, \"text\": \"acted before pictures emerged of his then-wife with a black eye.\"}, {\"start\": 42.54, \"end\": 58.6, \"text\": \"Sources tell CNN Chief of Staff John Kelly knew and White House counsel Don McGahn was\"}, {\"start\": 58.6, \"end\": 61.66, \"text\": \"made aware of the abuse allegations in the fall.\"}, {\"start\": 61.66, \"end\": 67.32, \"text\": \"President Trump is reportedly not happy about the unfolding scandal and is not sure how\"}, {\"start\": 67.32, \"end\": 69.5, \"text\": \"to handle the problem.\"}, {\"start\": 69.5, \"end\": 76.14, \"text\": \"He has spent the last two nights phoning friends and former aides for advice about how to handle\"}, {\"start\": 76.24, \"end\": 78.54, \"text\": \"the controversy.\"}, {\"start\": 78.54, \"end\": 82.44, \"text\": \"Porter has denied the allegations.\"}, {\"start\": 82.44, \"end\": 93.02, \"text\": \"But his ex-wife Jennifer Willoughby told CNN that when she spoke with Porter recently,\"}, {\"start\": 93.02, \"end\": 99.7, \"text\": \"he asked her to release a statement to downplay the abuse and to emphasize the relationship\"}, {\"start\": 99.7, \"end\": 103.22, \"text\": \"they have now as opposed to what she experienced during their marriage.\"}, {\"start\": 105.38, \"end\": 111.02, \"text\": \"There was a short government shutdown Friday in Washington.\"}, {\"start\": 111.02, \"end\": 119.5, \"text\": \"But Congress worked overnight to pass a two-year spending bill to keep the government open.\"}, {\"start\": 119.62, \"end\": 125.96, \"text\": \"The House voted 240-186.\"}, {\"start\": 125.96, \"end\": 134.64, \"text\": \"Republicans needed help from House Democrats to clear the bill and 73 Democrats gave it.\"}, {\"start\": 134.64, \"end\": 139.98, \"text\": \"But 67 House Republicans voted against the bill.\"}, {\"start\": 140.02, \"end\": 150.18, \"text\": \"The bill doles out $165 billion for the US military and increases the government spending\"}, {\"start\": 150.2, \"end\": 155.42, \"text\": \"cap by $300 billion.\"}, {\"start\": 155.42, \"end\": 165.18, \"text\": \"Noticeably missing from the bill, a long-term solution for DACA, which angered some House\"}, {\"start\": 165.18, \"end\": 167.34, \"text\": \"Democrats.\"}, {\"start\": 167.38, \"end\": 177.08, \"text\": \"But after the bill passed, Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell kept his word to open\"}, {\"start\": 177.08, \"end\": 179.8, \"text\": \"an immigration debate next week.\"}, {\"start\": 181.9, \"end\": 191.02, \"text\": \"There is no age requirement to run for office in Kansas.\"}, {\"start\": 191.02, \"end\": 201.46, \"text\": \"For that reason, six teenagers have filed papers to run for governor this November.\"}, {\"start\": 201.54, \"end\": 210.44, \"text\": \"Now Kansas lawmakers are trying to make sure something like this doesn't happen again.\"}, {\"start\": 210.44, \"end\": 223.1, \"text\": \"Republican Senator Blake Carpenter is introducing House Bill 2539 this week which states that\"}, {\"start\": 223.1, \"end\": 230.5, \"text\": \"candidates running for any government office in Kansas should be at least 18 years old\"}, {\"start\": 230.5, \"end\": 233.96, \"text\": \"and be a resident of the state for at least four consecutive years.\"}, {\"start\": 233.96, \"end\": 240.64, \"text\": \"However, if the proposed bill passes, it would not go into effect until 2019.\"}, {\"start\": 240.8, \"end\": 248.56, \"text\": \"That means the six teenagers can remain on the ballot.\"}, {\"start\": 250.64, \"end\": 266.16, \"text\": \"New research from the AAA Foundation for Traffic Safety found that drowsy drivers are a bigger\"}, {\"start\": 266.16, \"end\": 269.44, \"text\": \"road risk than previously thought.\"}, {\"start\": 269.44, \"end\": 275.12, \"text\": \"They not only put their lives at risk but also everyone else on the road.\"}, {\"start\": 275.12, \"end\": 283.92, \"text\": \"Accidents are three times greater during the nighttime hours where drowsiness was a factor.\"}, {\"start\": 283.92, \"end\": 296.16, \"text\": \"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention says an estimated 1 in 25 adult drivers has\"}, {\"start\": 296.16, \"end\": 298.45, \"text\": \"fallen asleep while driving in the past 30 days.\"}, {\"start\": 298.45, \"end\": 305.1, \"text\": \"The National Highway Traffic Safety Administration estimates that drowsy driving is responsible\"}, {\"start\": 305.1, \"end\": 316.2, \"text\": \"each year for about 83,000 crashes -- 37,000 of them with injuries and nearly 900 deaths.\"}, {\"start\": 316.2, \"end\": 328.64, \"text\": \"So if you're on the road, make sure you recognize the signs of drowsy driving.\"}, {\"start\": 328.64, \"end\": 345.12, \"text\": \"Yawning and blinking frequently, missing your exit and drifting from your lane.\"}, {\"start\": 345.12, \"end\": 351.2, \"text\": \"If you think you're too tired to drive, you probably are.\"}, {\"start\": 351.2, \"end\": 353.92, \"text\": \"So pullover.\"}, {\"start\": 353.92, \"end\": 358.24, \"text\": \"Better yet, don't get behind the wheel to begin with.\"}, {\"start\": 359.84, \"end\": 369.6, \"text\": \"You are looking at the world's first zero gravity dance party.\"}, {\"start\": 369.68, \"end\": 374.56, \"text\": \"It was a weightless dance party organized by \\\"Big-City Beats.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 374.56, \"end\": 380.56, \"text\": \"Ravers enjoyed up to 30 seconds of weightlessness.\"}, {\"start\": 380.56, \"end\": 389.36, \"text\": \"The venue was a customized Airbus A-310 that's usually used for astronaut training and scientific\"}, {\"start\": 389.84, \"end\": 392.8, \"text\": \"research.\"}, {\"start\": 392.88, \"end\": 400.96, \"text\": \"More than 30,000 people entered a contest to win a spot on the flight.\"}, {\"start\": 400.96, \"end\": 410.16, \"text\": \"Winners were chosen from countries like South Korea, Australia, England and the US.\"}, {\"start\": 412.08, \"end\": 434.08, \"text\": \"The sophomore class at Trier High School in Illinois has set not one, but two Guinness\"}, {\"start\": 434.08, \"end\": 438.0, \"text\": \"world records.\"}, {\"start\": 438.0, \"end\": 450.48, \"text\": \"The school's sophomore class has 44 sets of twins and one set of triplets.\"}, {\"start\": 450.48, \"end\": 459.32, \"text\": \"That's a record for the most twins and most multiples in a single academic year at one\"}, {\"start\": 459.32, \"end\": 460.9, \"text\": \"school.\"}, {\"start\": 462.82, \"end\": 465.08, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 465.08, \"end\": 466.74, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 466.74, \"end\": 468.96, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 468.96, \"end\": 473.68, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 473.68, \"end\": 479.98, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "0nhLqtKRRsk": {
    "video_id": "0nhLqtKRRsk",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.5.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180206",
    "duration": 609,
    "view_count": 1499,
    "description": "2.5.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\n-Trump calls Dems “treasonous” for State of the Union reaction (2.5.18)\n-Democrats push for release of second memo (2.5.18)\n-Nassar sentenced in 3rd trial (2.5.18)\n-Eagles fans go wild in Philly (2.5.18)\n-Super Bowl anti-terrorism documents left on plane (2.5.18)\n-Ram Truck ad using MLK speech sparks backlash (2.5.18)\n-Missing dog comes home after 10 years (2.5.18)\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital net",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.08, \"end\": 7.76, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.76, \"end\": 10.0, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.0, \"end\": 11.04, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 11.04, \"end\": 13.58, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.82, \"end\": 21.32, \"text\": \"President Trump is calling out some Democrats for their reaction to his first State of the\"}, {\"start\": 21.34, \"end\": 25.12, \"text\": \"Union speech last week.\"}, {\"start\": 25.12, \"end\": 37.34, \"text\": \"Trump said the stone-faced reactions he saw in the crowd may have even been \\\"treasonous.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 37.38, \"end\": 45.84, \"text\": \"He made the remarks Monday during a speech at a manufacturing plant in Cincinnati, Ohio.\"}, {\"start\": 45.84, \"end\": 51.0, \"text\": \"Trump added that some of the Democrats didn't seem to love the country that much and he\"}, {\"start\": 51.0, \"end\": 54.36, \"text\": \"called it \\\"very, very sad.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 54.36, \"end\": 62.16, \"text\": \"Trump also said the Democrats not sufficiently applauding his State of the Union address\"}, {\"start\": 62.16, \"end\": 65.94, \"text\": \"will make bipartisan cooperation more difficult.\"}, {\"start\": 65.98, \"end\": 73.5, \"text\": \"This is the second time Trump has brought attention to how Democrats reacted to his speech.\"}, {\"start\": 76.4, \"end\": 91.32, \"text\": \"The second chapter of Washington DC's memo saga could be coming soon.\"}, {\"start\": 91.32, \"end\": 95.2, \"text\": \"There is a push among Democrats, and some Republicans, to release a memo that rebuts\"}, {\"start\": 95.2, \"end\": 98.76, \"text\": \"allegations of FBI surveillance abuses.\"}, {\"start\": 98.76, \"end\": 100.96, \"text\": \"Democrats on the House Intelligence Committee may call for a vote Monday to release their\"}, {\"start\": 100.96, \"end\": 103.46, \"text\": \"memo on the FBI.\"}, {\"start\": 103.46, \"end\": 106.48, \"text\": \"This report is expected to contradict claims made in the Republican-led memo that was released\"}, {\"start\": 106.48, \"end\": 108.32, \"text\": \"Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 108.32, \"end\": 112.32, \"text\": \"Republicans blocked the release of the Democratic memo last week but have since said they'd\"}, {\"start\": 112.32, \"end\": 114.62, \"text\": \"vote to released the memo.\"}, {\"start\": 114.62, \"end\": 123.96, \"text\": \"Senator Chuck Schumer is calling on President Trump to back the release of the second memo,\"}, {\"start\": 123.96, \"end\": 129.48, \"text\": \"saying it is \\\"a matter of fundamental fairness.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 129.64, \"end\": 133.4, \"text\": \"And some Republicans are on board.\"}, {\"start\": 133.4, \"end\": 136.92, \"text\": \"If the committee votes in favor of putting out the memo, the issue then goes to President\"}, {\"start\": 136.92, \"end\": 138.68, \"text\": \"Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 138.68, \"end\": 145.48, \"text\": \"He would have five days to make a decision on the release.\"}, {\"start\": 149.2, \"end\": 157.52, \"text\": \"On Monday former USA gymnastics and Michigan State doctor Larry Nassar was sentenced in\"}, {\"start\": 157.68, \"end\": 162.12, \"text\": \"his third sexual abuse trial.\"}, {\"start\": 162.12, \"end\": 168.48, \"text\": \"The judge sentenced him to 40 to 125 years in prison for sexually abusing young girls\"}, {\"start\": 168.6, \"end\": 171.56, \"text\": \"for more than two decades.\"}, {\"start\": 171.56, \"end\": 175.56, \"text\": \"He's expected to spend the rest of his life in prison.\"}, {\"start\": 175.56, \"end\": 183.68, \"text\": \"But as Nassar goes away, the follow up from his trial continues.\"}, {\"start\": 183.72, \"end\": 190.28, \"text\": \"Michigan State University and USA gymnastics have been forced to change leadership.\"}, {\"start\": 190.28, \"end\": 195.04, \"text\": \"Multiple investigations are expected, with Michigan State University being targeted by\"}, {\"start\": 195.04, \"end\": 199.64, \"text\": \"both the state Attorney General and the NCAA.\"}, {\"start\": 199.64, \"end\": 204.24, \"text\": \"The US Olympic Committee is also calling for an investigation by an independent third-party\"}, {\"start\": 204.24, \"end\": 209.56, \"text\": \"to find out how abuse of this proportion could have gone undetected for so long.\"}, {\"start\": 209.56, \"end\": 216.0, \"text\": \"Everyone involved has denied they helped cover up the abuse.\"}, {\"start\": 219.36, \"end\": 224.68, \"text\": \"Congratulations to the Philadelphia Eagles for winning their first Super Bowl championship\"}, {\"start\": 224.8, \"end\": 227.12, \"text\": \"in franchise history!\"}, {\"start\": 227.12, \"end\": 232.12, \"text\": \"The Eagles pulled off an exciting victory Sunday night over the New England Patriots,\"}, {\"start\": 232.12, \"end\": 234.24, \"text\": \"44-33.\"}, {\"start\": 234.24, \"end\": 239.56, \"text\": \"Eagles quarterback Nick Foles was named Super Bowl MVP.\"}, {\"start\": 239.56, \"end\": 247.36, \"text\": \"City officials confirmed that the parade will be held on Thursday around 11 AM.\"}, {\"start\": 247.44, \"end\": 256.6, \"text\": \"The parade will begin at Broad and Pattison in south Philadelphia, then head north to\"}, {\"start\": 256.6, \"end\": 258.56, \"text\": \"the art museum.\"}, {\"start\": 258.56, \"end\": 263.04, \"text\": \"But many fans started the celebration early.\"}, {\"start\": 263.04, \"end\": 266.28, \"text\": \"Right after the win, the city went wild!\"}, {\"start\": 266.28, \"end\": 269.12, \"text\": \"Most of the celebrations were good, clean fun.\"}, {\"start\": 269.12, \"end\": 273.96, \"text\": \"But there were also incidents of vandalism and looting.\"}, {\"start\": 273.96, \"end\": 279.72, \"text\": \"Police say there were reports of flipped cars, a Christmas tree fire and people climbing\"}, {\"start\": 279.76, \"end\": 288.16, \"text\": \"statues and traffic light poles.\"}, {\"start\": 288.36, \"end\": 293.4, \"text\": \"Officials say three people were arrested in disturbances around the city.\"}, {\"start\": 297.2, \"end\": 304.04, \"text\": \"The Department of Homeland Security documents\"}, {\"start\": 304.04, \"end\": 312.2, \"text\": \"were found in the seat back pocket of a commercial airplane.\"}, {\"start\": 312.2, \"end\": 322.92, \"text\": \"Most of the documents were marked \\\"For Official Use Only.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 322.92, \"end\": 331.6, \"text\": \"The documents detailed anti-terrorism preparations for Sunday\"}, {\"start\": 331.6, \"end\": 351.8, \"text\": \"night's Super Bowl -- 78 pages containing details of preparations in the event of a\"}, {\"start\": 351.8, \"end\": 370.2, \"text\": \"biological attack.\"}, {\"start\": 370.24, \"end\": 374.24, \"text\": \"The document also spelled out specific instructions on how to safeguard the document.\"}, {\"start\": 374.24, \"end\": 381.52, \"text\": \"It said the document should be stored in a locked drawer after business hours, the contents\"}, {\"start\": 381.52, \"end\": 388.0, \"text\": \"should not be shared with individuals who do not have operational \\\"need-to-know\\\" and\"}, {\"start\": 388.0, \"end\": 395.36, \"text\": \"the document should be shredded before discarding.\"}, {\"start\": 395.36, \"end\": 402.88, \"text\": \"And the document included the travel itinerary of a senior manager at DHS, the man in charge\"}, {\"start\": 403.2, \"end\": 416.0, \"text\": \"of the government's detection and response to a bio-terror attack.\"}, {\"start\": 416.0, \"end\": 424.4, \"text\": \"CNN was unable to verify who left the documents on the plane but the travel itinerary and\"}, {\"start\": 424.4, \"end\": 435.44, \"text\": \"boarding pass accompanying the documents were in the name of Michael V. Walter.\"}, {\"start\": 435.44, \"end\": 441.44, \"text\": \"According to his LinkedIn profile, Walter is a microbiologist and has been the program\"}, {\"start\": 441.44, \"end\": 445.6, \"text\": \"manager of \\\"Bio-Watch\\\" since 2009.\"}, {\"start\": 450.0, \"end\": 458.72, \"text\": \"The Dodge Ram Super Bowl commercial is sparking some criticism.\"}, {\"start\": 458.72, \"end\": 468.72, \"text\": \"The ad features a Martin Luther King Jr. speech from 50 years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 468.72, \"end\": 474.32, \"text\": \"It has scenes of kids playing, fishermen, members of the military, a teacher and students\"}, {\"start\": 474.32, \"end\": 476.56, \"text\": \"and a firefighter.\"}, {\"start\": 476.56, \"end\": 483.84, \"text\": \"King can be heard saying: \\\"But recognize that he who is greatest among you shall be your\"}, {\"start\": 483.84, \"end\": 486.4, \"text\": \"servant.\"}, {\"start\": 486.4, \"end\": 490.16, \"text\": \"That's the new definition of greatness.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 490.4, \"end\": 499.36, \"text\": \"At the end of the ad, Rams' slogan \\\"Built To Serve\\\" appears on the screen.\"}, {\"start\": 499.6, \"end\": 505.52, \"text\": \"Some viewers felt it was distasteful to use a civil rights leader's speech to advertise\"}, {\"start\": 505.92, \"end\": 508.16, \"text\": \"trucks.\"}, {\"start\": 508.16, \"end\": 514.08, \"text\": \"The King estate said in a statement it had \\\"reviewed the ad before it aired to make sure\"}, {\"start\": 514.32, \"end\": 518.32, \"text\": \"it met its standards.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 518.56, \"end\": 528.8, \"text\": \"And Fiat Chrysler, which owns Ram, said in a statement: \\\"The company worked closely with\"}, {\"start\": 528.8, \"end\": 532.4, \"text\": \"the representatives of the Martin Luther King Jr. estate to receive the necessary approvals.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 535.2, \"end\": 550.52, \"text\": \"Ten years ago Debra Suierveld says her dog, Abby, went outside to play in the woods near\"}, {\"start\": 550.52, \"end\": 551.44, \"text\": \"their Apollo, PA home.\"}, {\"start\": 551.44, \"end\": 552.64, \"text\": \"She never came back.\"}, {\"start\": 552.64, \"end\": 560.78, \"text\": \"The family had all but given up on ever seeing her again.\"}, {\"start\": 560.78, \"end\": 568.56, \"text\": \"Then on January 28th Abby showed up on the doorstep of a home about 10 miles away.\"}, {\"start\": 568.56, \"end\": 574.78, \"text\": \"The homeowner called the authorities and Abby was identified by her microchip.\"}, {\"start\": 574.96, \"end\": 577.1, \"text\": \"The Suiervelds says they have no idea where Abby has been for the past 10 years and they\"}, {\"start\": 577.1, \"end\": 578.1, \"text\": \"don't care.\"}, {\"start\": 578.22, \"end\": 580.22, \"text\": \"They're just happy she's back where she belongs.\"}, {\"start\": 582.38, \"end\": 585.34, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 585.34, \"end\": 586.82, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 586.82, \"end\": 589.76, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 589.76, \"end\": 594.24, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 594.24, \"end\": 600.96, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "BaMqQQIlBbM": {
    "video_id": "BaMqQQIlBbM",
    "title": "Police investigate massive brawl on cruise ship (ASL - 2.18.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180219",
    "duration": 98,
    "view_count": 262,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.7, \"end\": 6.18, \"text\": \"We have the video of a massive brawl that broke out on a cruise ship.\"}, {\"start\": 6.18, \"end\": 13.42, \"text\": \"The 10-day Carnival cruise was headed to the South Pacific.\"}, {\"start\": 13.42, \"end\": 18.92, \"text\": \"Vicious brawls broke out over several days.\"}, {\"start\": 18.92, \"end\": 23.24, \"text\": \"Witnesses say it was horrifying.\"}, {\"start\": 23.24, \"end\": 30.64, \"text\": \"People were screaming, running, throwing glasses and blood was everywhere.\"}, {\"start\": 30.64, \"end\": 37.64, \"text\": \"Some passengers blame one group of 23 people who were traveling together, claiming the\"}, {\"start\": 37.649, \"end\": 43.93, \"text\": \"group was picking on any Australian person they could find.\"}, {\"start\": 43.93, \"end\": 49.71, \"text\": \"Others blame the ship security guards, claiming they were kicking passengers and punching\"}, {\"start\": 49.71, \"end\": 51.54, \"text\": \"women and children.\"}, {\"start\": 51.54, \"end\": 53.22, \"text\": \"See for yourself.\"}, {\"start\": 79.74, \"end\": 86.56, \"text\": \"The ship had to turn around and head back to Melbourne, Australia.\"}, {\"start\": 86.56, \"end\": 91.6, \"text\": \"Nine passengers were forced off the ship.\"}, {\"start\": 91.6, \"end\": 94.06, \"text\": \"Several passengers are demanding a refund.\"}, {\"start\": 94.06, \"end\": 97.38, \"text\": \"Others say they plan to sue.\"}]"
  },
  "r98gHFIKtNE": {
    "video_id": "r98gHFIKtNE",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.2.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180402",
    "duration": 585,
    "view_count": 1518,
    "description": "4.2.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Teachers walk out in Oklahoma & Kentucky\n-Doctors shocked by 30lb tumor in man’s abdomen\n-“Affluenza” teen released from jail\n-China hits U.S. with $38B in tariffs\n-“The Rock” opens up about his battle with depression\n-Winnie Mandela dead at 81\n-140th White House Easter Egg Roll\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrou",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.16, \"end\": 9.5, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.5, \"end\": 11.94, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.96, \"end\": 13.64, \"text\": \"I’m Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 13.64, \"end\": 16.68, \"text\": \"Here your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.46, \"end\": 27.44, \"text\": \"Last month thousands of teachers in West Virginia walked off the job, demanding a pay raise.\"}, {\"start\": 27.44, \"end\": 29.8, \"text\": \"And they got it.\"}, {\"start\": 29.8, \"end\": 40.56, \"text\": \"Now teachers in Oklahoma and Kentucky are doing the same.\"}, {\"start\": 40.66, \"end\": 47.02, \"text\": \"In Kentucky, teachers and their supporters came together for a rally Monday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 47.02, \"end\": 52.04, \"text\": \"They marched to the state Capitol, protesting a controversial bill that passed the state\"}, {\"start\": 52.04, \"end\": 54.22, \"text\": \"legislature last week.\"}, {\"start\": 54.22, \"end\": 61.12, \"text\": \"The bill makes big changes to the state’s pension system, which affects teachers.\"}, {\"start\": 61.12, \"end\": 71.32, \"text\": \"After that bill passed, teachers called out of work last Friday, causing school closures\"}, {\"start\": 71.34, \"end\": 74.36, \"text\": \"across the state.\"}, {\"start\": 74.36, \"end\": 85.46, \"text\": \"Teachers in Oklahoma are rallying for more education funding and salaries.\"}, {\"start\": 85.48, \"end\": 89.36, \"text\": \"Some teachers say they are struggling to make ends meet so they work two jobs, sell their\"}, {\"start\": 89.36, \"end\": 96.52, \"text\": \"blood, mow lawns or eat at soup kitchens.\"}, {\"start\": 96.52, \"end\": 101.56, \"text\": \"All the schools across the state are closed because of the dispute, including Oklahoma\"}, {\"start\": 101.56, \"end\": 103.84, \"text\": \"City Public schools.\"}, {\"start\": 105.6, \"end\": 110.32, \"text\": \"We want to warn you: this story contains an image that some viewers may find disturbing\"}, {\"start\": 110.32, \"end\": 112.96, \"text\": \"due to its graphic nature.\"}, {\"start\": 112.96, \"end\": 120.84, \"text\": \"Kevin Daly is an athletic, healthy 62-year-old man.\"}, {\"start\": 120.84, \"end\": 130.88, \"text\": \"But up until a few months ago, Daly couldn’t get rid of what everyone thought was a beer belly.\"}, {\"start\": 130.88, \"end\": 134.4, \"text\": \"Oddly enough, Daly doesn’t even drink beer.\"}, {\"start\": 134.4, \"end\": 139.42, \"text\": \"And he recently lost 35 pounds after heart surgery.\"}, {\"start\": 139.42, \"end\": 141.9, \"text\": \"But his belly didn’t shrink.\"}, {\"start\": 141.9, \"end\": 148.76, \"text\": \"Daly finally convinced his insurance company to pay for a CAT scan.\"}, {\"start\": 148.76, \"end\": 152.24, \"text\": \"Turns out his beer belly was actually a huge tumor taking up most of his abdominal cavity.\"}, {\"start\": 152.24, \"end\": 155.72, \"text\": \"He was scheduled for surgery right away.\"}, {\"start\": 155.72, \"end\": 165.52, \"text\": \"It took six hours but doctors were able to get the tumor out in one piece.\"}, {\"start\": 165.64, \"end\": 168.56, \"text\": \"The tumor weighed 30 pounds!\"}, {\"start\": 168.56, \"end\": 175.0, \"text\": \"It was also wrapped around Daly’s kidney so it had to be removed as well.\"}, {\"start\": 175.0, \"end\": 180.88, \"text\": \"Despite the size of the tumor, Daly never once experienced any symptoms.\"}, {\"start\": 181.16, \"end\": 186.72, \"text\": \"But now two months later, Daly says he’s feeling great and very lucky.\"}, {\"start\": 188.64, \"end\": 200.68, \"text\": \"Back in June 2013, 20-year-old Ethan Couch drove a pickup truck while drunk and crashed\"}, {\"start\": 200.68, \"end\": 203.88, \"text\": \"into four pedestrians, killing them.\"}, {\"start\": 203.88, \"end\": 212.88, \"text\": \"His attorney argued that Couch was a victim of “affluenza,” that his wealthy, privileged\"}, {\"start\": 212.88, \"end\": 217.24, \"text\": \"upbringing had made it impossible for him to understand that his actions have consequences.\"}, {\"start\": 217.24, \"end\": 224.12, \"text\": \"Prosecutors wanted Couch to serve 20 years in jail but because he was a teenager at\"}, {\"start\": 224.16, \"end\": 230.72, \"text\": \"the time, a juvenile judge only sentenced him to probation.\"}, {\"start\": 230.72, \"end\": 239.32, \"text\": \"That decision outraged the victims’ families and anti-drunk driving advocates.\"}, {\"start\": 239.32, \"end\": 247.24, \"text\": \"Then in 2015, Couch violated the terms of his probation and fled to Mexico with his mother.\"}, {\"start\": 247.24, \"end\": 253.64, \"text\": \"After he was caught and brought back to the US, a Texas judge sentenced Couch to two years\"}, {\"start\": 253.72, \"end\": 255.56, \"text\": \"in jail.\"}, {\"start\": 255.56, \"end\": 258.4, \"text\": \"Today Couch was released from jail.\"}, {\"start\": 258.4, \"end\": 265.92, \"text\": \"As part of his current probation, he will be required to wear an ankle monitor and an alcohol\"}, {\"start\": 265.92, \"end\": 271.84, \"text\": \"detecting patch and abide by a 9 PM curfew.\"}, {\"start\": 273.4, \"end\": 281.16, \"text\": \"China is making good on its trade threats.\"}, {\"start\": 281.16, \"end\": 291.36, \"text\": \"The Chinese government says that tariffs of about $3 billion worth of US imports will\"}, {\"start\": 291.36, \"end\": 298.88, \"text\": \"go into effect today, impacting roughly 128 products.\"}, {\"start\": 298.88, \"end\": 308.16, \"text\": \"The sanctions are in response to President Trump’s tariffs on imports of steel and\"}, {\"start\": 308.16, \"end\": 312.96, \"text\": \"aluminum.\"}, {\"start\": 312.96, \"end\": 324.32, \"text\": \"China plans to impose tariffs of 15% on items such as fruit, nuts, wine and steel pipes.\"}, {\"start\": 324.32, \"end\": 332.48, \"text\": \"And tariffs of 25% on items like pork and recycled aluminum.\"}, {\"start\": 332.48, \"end\": 336.16, \"text\": \"China has repeatedly said it wants to avoid a trade war.\"}, {\"start\": 336.16, \"end\": 341.76, \"text\": \"But warned that it will take necessary countermeasures to defend its interests.\"}, {\"start\": 344.32, \"end\": 359.84, \"text\": \"Actor Dwayne “The Rock” Johnson revealed in an interview that he battles depression\"}, {\"start\": 359.84, \"end\": 363.84, \"text\": \"and times have been harder for him than fans know.\"}, {\"start\": 363.84, \"end\": 371.68, \"text\": \"He says he went through a dark period years ago when injuries ended his dreams of playing\"}, {\"start\": 371.68, \"end\": 373.18, \"text\": \"professional football.\"}, {\"start\": 373.18, \"end\": 380.64, \"text\": \"And around the same time, his then-girlfriend broke up with him.\"}, {\"start\": 380.64, \"end\": 389.76, \"text\": \"However the worst time came when he was 15 years old and his mother attempted suicide.\"}, {\"start\": 389.76, \"end\": 397.76, \"text\": \"Johnson said his mother got out of their car on the interstate and attempted to walk into\"}, {\"start\": 397.76, \"end\": 403.2, \"text\": \"oncoming traffic.\"}, {\"start\": 403.2, \"end\": 407.2, \"text\": \"Johnson saved her life by pulling her back to the side of the road.\"}, {\"start\": 407.2, \"end\": 414.4, \"text\": \"He says he and his mother both have gone on to find happiness and he is now using his\"}, {\"start\": 414.4, \"end\": 420.16, \"text\": \"experiences to try and help others struggling with depression.\"}, {\"start\": 422.24, \"end\": 437.28, \"text\": \"Anti-apartheid icon Winnie Mandela has died at the age of 81.\"}, {\"start\": 437.28, \"end\": 444.8, \"text\": \"She was the former wife of South Africa’s late president Nelson Mandela.\"}, {\"start\": 444.8, \"end\": 451.68, \"text\": \"According to a family statement, her health began to fail early this year and she died\"}, {\"start\": 451.68, \"end\": 458.88, \"text\": \"at a Johannesburg hospital Monday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 458.88, \"end\": 466.56, \"text\": \"She spent time behind bars fighting for the cause and kept Nelson Mandela’s memory alive\"}, {\"start\": 466.56, \"end\": 475.52, \"text\": \"during his more than 27 years in prison.\"}, {\"start\": 475.52, \"end\": 480.32, \"text\": \"Along with her former husband, Winnie Mandela became one of the most recognizable faces\"}, {\"start\": 480.32, \"end\": 487.36, \"text\": \"in the decades-long struggle to end apartheid.\"}, {\"start\": 488.96, \"end\": 493.76, \"text\": \"There was a huge Easter egg party at the White House this morning.\"}, {\"start\": 493.76, \"end\": 511.16, \"text\": \"First lady Melania Trump hosted the 140th annual Easter Egg Roll on the White House’s\"}, {\"start\": 511.16, \"end\": 513.74, \"text\": \"South lawn.\"}, {\"start\": 513.74, \"end\": 520.32, \"text\": \"Those who took part in this morning’s roll were winners of a public lottery held earlier\"}, {\"start\": 520.32, \"end\": 523.84, \"text\": \"this year.\"}, {\"start\": 523.84, \"end\": 532.0, \"text\": \"Activities included lawn bowling, reading area, card-making station for troops, egg\"}, {\"start\": 532.0, \"end\": 538.4, \"text\": \"and cookie decorating stations and the main event – the egg roll.\"}, {\"start\": 538.4, \"end\": 542.08, \"text\": \"About 30,000 people attended the event.\"}, {\"start\": 542.08, \"end\": 553.6, \"text\": \"The tradition started 140 years ago during the Rutherford B. Hayes administration.\"}, {\"start\": 557.76, \"end\": 560.32, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 560.32, \"end\": 561.64, \"text\": \"I’m Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 561.64, \"end\": 564.56, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 564.56, \"end\": 570.08, \"text\": \"Remember to like this on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 570.08, \"end\": 577.68, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "VSG2Q4h7WrQ": {
    "video_id": "VSG2Q4h7WrQ",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.3.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180104",
    "duration": 680,
    "view_count": 1370,
    "description": "1.3.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-TRUMP WAR OF WORDS WITH N. KOREA ESCALATES\n-TRUMP UNLOADS ON BANNON, SAYS HE LOST HIS MIND\n-PENCE SWEARS IN DOUG JONES AND TINA SMITH\n-WINTER WEATHER IS ABOUT TO GET WORSE\n-NISSAN WORKING ON MIND-READING CARS\n-GENERAL MILLS RELEASING NEW CEREAL MASH-UPS\n-LOTTERY JACKPOT KEEPS GROWING\n-DADDY-DAUGHTER \"SINGLE LADIES\" DANCE GOES VIRAL\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.84, \"end\": 6.62, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.62, \"end\": 8.1, \"text\": \"Welcome Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.1, \"end\": 9.08, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 9.08, \"end\": 11.12, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 12.84, \"end\": 22.28, \"text\": \"Earlier this week we told you how North Korean leader Kim Jong Un bragged that he had a nuclear\"}, {\"start\": 22.28, \"end\": 28.88, \"text\": \"weapon on his desk and the United States is always within range of a North Korean strike.\"}, {\"start\": 28.88, \"end\": 36.28, \"text\": \"Today President Trump responded in a tweet by taunting Kim Jong Un.\"}, {\"start\": 36.28, \"end\": 46.14, \"text\": \"Trump said that his nuclear button is \\\"much bigger and more powerful\\\" than North Korea's\"}, {\"start\": 46.14, \"end\": 51.06, \"text\": \"and then added a threat: the US button works.\"}, {\"start\": 51.06, \"end\": 60.3, \"text\": \"Some military officials say this type of taunting is cause for alarm because no one knows Kim\"}, {\"start\": 60.3, \"end\": 65.34, \"text\": \"Jong Un's ignition point.\"}, {\"start\": 65.34, \"end\": 76.48, \"text\": \"Any one of these tweets could set him off and cause him to hit the nuclear button, potentially\"}, {\"start\": 76.48, \"end\": 79.88, \"text\": \"killing millions.\"}, {\"start\": 82.34, \"end\": 88.3, \"text\": \"A new book entitled \\\"Fire and Fury\\\" was just released.\"}, {\"start\": 88.3, \"end\": 103.56, \"text\": \"A copy of the book was obtained by the newspaper \\\"The Guardian.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 103.58, \"end\": 116.92, \"text\": \"In the book former White House chief strategist Steve Bannon reportedly said the 2016 meeting\"}, {\"start\": 116.92, \"end\": 131.98, \"text\": \"between Trump campaign officials and a Russian lawyer was \\\"treasonous.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 131.98, \"end\": 137.2, \"text\": \"Bannon told the book's author that they should have immediately called the FBI.\"}, {\"start\": 137.2, \"end\": 160.72, \"text\": \"Jared Kushner, Donald Trump, Jr and then-campaign chairman Paul Manafort were present.\"}, {\"start\": 160.76, \"end\": 166.8, \"text\": \"The Russian lawyer purportedly offered campaign officials damaging information on\"}, {\"start\": 166.8, \"end\": 170.96, \"text\": \"Hillary Clinton.\"}, {\"start\": 170.96, \"end\": 182.84, \"text\": \"President Trump immediately released a blistering statement slamming Bannon.\"}, {\"start\": 182.88, \"end\": 189.84, \"text\": \"Trump said when Bannon was fired, he not only lost his job, he lost his mind.\"}, {\"start\": 189.84, \"end\": 193.2, \"text\": \"Trump also wrote that Bannon, who led the Trump campaign for a time, had very little\"}, {\"start\": 193.2, \"end\": 198.6, \"text\": \"to do with his election victory.\"}, {\"start\": 198.6, \"end\": 211.2, \"text\": \"He also blamed Bannon for the defeat of Alabama GOP Senate candidate Roy Moore and accused\"}, {\"start\": 211.2, \"end\": 222.84, \"text\": \"Bannon of using his White House job to leak false information.\"}, {\"start\": 225.44, \"end\": 238.16, \"text\": \"Today Vice President Mike Pence swore in senators Doug Jones of Alabama and Tina Smith of Minnesota.\"}, {\"start\": 238.28, \"end\": 247.72, \"text\": \"Jones won last month's special election, a rarity for a Democrat in a traditionally Republican\"}, {\"start\": 247.72, \"end\": 250.24, \"text\": \"state.\"}, {\"start\": 250.24, \"end\": 257.12, \"text\": \"He beat controversial Republican candidate Roy Moore, who's been accused of sexual misconduct\"}, {\"start\": 257.28, \"end\": 261.4, \"text\": \"by several women when they were in their teens.\"}, {\"start\": 261.4, \"end\": 269.36, \"text\": \"Smith is the temporary replacement for former Senator Al Franken who formally resigned Tuesday\"}, {\"start\": 269.4, \"end\": 274.48, \"text\": \"in the wake of multiple sexual harassment allegations.\"}, {\"start\": 274.48, \"end\": 281.24, \"text\": \"A special election will be held in November to fill out the final two years of Franken's\"}, {\"start\": 281.24, \"end\": 284.8, \"text\": \"term.\"}, {\"start\": 287.08, \"end\": 295.8, \"text\": \"Forecasters say the winter weather hitting the country is about to get a whole lot worse.\"}, {\"start\": 296.04, \"end\": 302.56, \"text\": \"One third of the United States is experiencing dangerous subzero temperatures.\"}, {\"start\": 302.56, \"end\": 307.92, \"text\": \"The punishing chill is even hitting as far south as Alabama and Florida..\"}, {\"start\": 307.92, \"end\": 316.24, \"text\": \"More than 100 million Americans are under windchill advisories.\"}, {\"start\": 316.24, \"end\": 322.96, \"text\": \"And there have already been 12 deaths nationwide related to the cold weather.\"}, {\"start\": 322.96, \"end\": 329.68, \"text\": \"Officials in many states have warned people not to be out on the roads unless it is absolutely\"}, {\"start\": 329.68, \"end\": 332.52, \"text\": \"necessary.\"}, {\"start\": 332.52, \"end\": 340.92, \"text\": \"Many states are preparing shelters and warning residents to stay indoors as they brace for\"}, {\"start\": 340.92, \"end\": 344.16, \"text\": \"ice and snow.\"}, {\"start\": 344.16, \"end\": 351.96, \"text\": \"If the power goes out, officials are telling people to find the nearest shelter and have\"}, {\"start\": 351.96, \"end\": 355.56, \"text\": \"an emergency plan in place.\"}, {\"start\": 355.56, \"end\": 366.44, \"text\": \"But if you are planning to rely on a generator, please remember *do not* use it indoors.\"}, {\"start\": 368.84, \"end\": 377.64, \"text\": \"Many companies are working on cars that drive themselves using computers.\"}, {\"start\": 377.64, \"end\": 387.76, \"text\": \"But Nissan engineers are researching technology that uses brainwave sensors to detect what\"}, {\"start\": 387.76, \"end\": 393.16, \"text\": \"a driver intends to do in the next fraction of a second.\"}, {\"start\": 393.16, \"end\": 402.48, \"text\": \"Engineers believe that the brain-to-vehicle technology could shorten reaction times.\"}, {\"start\": 402.48, \"end\": 412.04, \"text\": \"For example sensors could detect the driver's intention to slam on the brakes.\"}, {\"start\": 412.04, \"end\": 417.76, \"text\": \"The brakes would then be applied immediately even before the driver's foot has touched\"}, {\"start\": 417.76, \"end\": 420.8, \"text\": \"the brake pedal.\"}, {\"start\": 420.8, \"end\": 425.72, \"text\": \"Nissan says it hopes to have some version of this technology ready for real world use\"}, {\"start\": 425.72, \"end\": 429.48, \"text\": \"in 5 to 10 years.\"}, {\"start\": 431.52, \"end\": 446.76, \"text\": \"Check out General Mills's three new mashup cereals.\"}, {\"start\": 446.76, \"end\": 463.56, \"text\": \"They are Peanut Butter Chocolate Blasted Shreds, Lucky Charms Frosted Flakes and Cinnamon Toast\"}, {\"start\": 463.56, \"end\": 469.52, \"text\": \"Crunch Blasted Shreds.\"}, {\"start\": 469.52, \"end\": 477.24, \"text\": \"The \\\"shreds\\\" cereal are essentially sweeter versions of Mini-Wheats.\"}, {\"start\": 477.24, \"end\": 490.16, \"text\": \"But it's the Lucky Charms Frosted Flakes mashup that has people talking.\"}, {\"start\": 490.16, \"end\": 507.96, \"text\": \"General Mills cereal rival Kellogg's has made Frosted Flakes cereal for decades.\"}, {\"start\": 507.96, \"end\": 513.2, \"text\": \"That leaves people to wonder if Kellogg's and General Mills are joining forces.\"}, {\"start\": 513.2, \"end\": 514.48, \"text\": \"The answer is \\\"no.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 514.48, \"end\": 528.56, \"text\": \"Frosted Flakes is not a trademarked term so any cereal company can make its own version.\"}, {\"start\": 528.56, \"end\": 535.92, \"text\": \"The cereal mashups are expected to roll out later this year.\"}, {\"start\": 538.2, \"end\": 544.84, \"text\": \"The lottery jackpot numbers just keep climbing.\"}, {\"start\": 544.84, \"end\": 560.0, \"text\": \"Both the Powerball and Mega Millions jackpot is now over the $400 million mark.\"}, {\"start\": 560.0, \"end\": 567.36, \"text\": \"Tonight's Powerball jackpot is worth at least $440 million.\"}, {\"start\": 567.36, \"end\": 572.8, \"text\": \"And that number is expected to go up before the drawing.\"}, {\"start\": 572.8, \"end\": 582.08, \"text\": \"If there's no big winner, it will roll over again to Saturday night.\"}, {\"start\": 582.12, \"end\": 590.2, \"text\": \"And no one won the Mega Millions jackpot in Tuesday's drawing.\"}, {\"start\": 590.2, \"end\": 596.2, \"text\": \"That jackpot is now up to at least $418 million.\"}, {\"start\": 596.2, \"end\": 598.8, \"text\": \"The next Mega Millions drawing is Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 601.08, \"end\": 609.8, \"text\": \"This video of a Michigan dad is going viral.\"}, {\"start\": 609.88, \"end\": 625.12, \"text\": \"Steve Haddad's family tradition is to do a Christmas lip-sync battle.\"}, {\"start\": 625.12, \"end\": 636.68, \"text\": \"This year Haddad and his daughters performed Beyonce's \\\"Single Ladies.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 636.68, \"end\": 646.84, \"text\": \"But Haddad took it a step further and wore the leotard from the music video.\"}, {\"start\": 646.96, \"end\": 652.88, \"text\": \"He even learned the dance routine from a professional choreographer.\"}, {\"start\": 652.96, \"end\": 657.96, \"text\": \"The video has more than 21 million views on Facebook.\"}, {\"start\": 659.56, \"end\": 661.96, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 661.96, \"end\": 663.24, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 663.24, \"end\": 665.04, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 665.04, \"end\": 668.96, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 669.12, \"end\": 674.24, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "lFUWngaOlIc": {
    "video_id": "lFUWngaOlIc",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.8.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180409",
    "duration": 615,
    "view_count": 1140,
    "description": "4.8.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Syria chemical attack kills dozens\n-Caravan of migrants closer to the U.S. border\n-One dead, several hurt in Trump Tower fire\n-Al Sharpton, Parkland student announce march\n-Father confesses to killing autistic son\n-Weekend box office\n-National Pet Day\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizatio",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.48, \"end\": 8.94, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.94, \"end\": 10.58, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.64, \"end\": 12.82, \"text\": \"I’m Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.82, \"end\": 15.68, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.32, \"end\": 25.88, \"text\": \"We have received disturbing video from the Eastern Ghouta in Syria.\"}, {\"start\": 25.88, \"end\": 37.11, \"text\": \"Sadly the video shows many people who activists say were attacked by a suspected chemical agent.\"}, {\"start\": 37.11, \"end\": 43.3, \"text\": \"According to local doctors, dozens have died and many more could be dead.\"}, {\"start\": 43.3, \"end\": 51.22, \"text\": \"We must warn you: the video you’re about to see contains very graphic images.\"}, {\"start\": 51.22, \"end\": 57.76, \"text\": \"If you don’t want to see it, please fast-forward to the next story.\"}, {\"start\": 81.48, \"end\": 91.3, \"text\": \"Those were men, women and children from Douma in Eastern Ghouta.\"}, {\"start\": 91.3, \"end\": 94.3, \"text\": \"Their bodies were strewn on the floor of their underground shelter.\"}, {\"start\": 94.3, \"end\": 100.4, \"text\": \"Their faces were ghost white, some with eyes still open, with expressions of shock and\"}, {\"start\": 100.4, \"end\": 103.02, \"text\": \"of violent death.\"}, {\"start\": 103.04, \"end\": 110.98, \"text\": \"What you see off their mouths and noses appear to be foam, a telltale sign of a chemical agent.\"}, {\"start\": 110.98, \"end\": 114.64, \"text\": \"This is not the first time of reports of a chemical attack in Syria.\"}, {\"start\": 114.64, \"end\": 120.96, \"text\": \"The country has been accused of it on at least three other occasions in the last six years.\"}, {\"start\": 120.96, \"end\": 125.28, \"text\": \"The Syrian government denies being behind this incident.\"}, {\"start\": 125.28, \"end\": 131.52, \"text\": \"Political leaders around the world have condemned the attack.\"}, {\"start\": 131.52, \"end\": 138.0, \"text\": \"President Trump tweeted about the attack on Sunday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 147.52, \"text\": \"In a rare criticism by name, he specifically called out Russian President Vladimir Putin\"}, {\"start\": 147.52, \"end\": 161.68, \"text\": \"for his country’s support of Syrian President Bashar al-Assad saying: “Many dead, including\"}, {\"start\": 161.68, \"end\": 166.56, \"text\": \"women and children, in mindless chemical attack in Syria.\"}, {\"start\": 166.56, \"end\": 173.92, \"text\": \"Area of atrocity is in lockdown and encircled by Syrian army, making it completely inaccessible\"}, {\"start\": 173.92, \"end\": 175.6, \"text\": \"to outside world.\"}, {\"start\": 175.6, \"end\": 185.2, \"text\": \"President Putin, Russia and Iran are responsible for backing animal Assad.\"}, {\"start\": 185.2, \"end\": 187.38, \"text\": \"Big picture…to pay.\"}, {\"start\": 187.38, \"end\": 192.26, \"text\": \"Open area immediately for medical help and verification.\"}, {\"start\": 192.28, \"end\": 194.64, \"text\": \"Another humanitarian disaster for no reason whatsoever.\"}, {\"start\": 194.68, \"end\": 196.42, \"text\": \"Sick!”\"}, {\"start\": 200.2, \"end\": 205.8, \"text\": \"The first busload of migrants traveling toward the US border as part of an annual caravan\"}, {\"start\": 205.8, \"end\": 210.3, \"text\": \"has arrived in Puebla, Mexico.\"}, {\"start\": 210.3, \"end\": 219.22, \"text\": \"The annual pilgrimage includes people who’ve come together to head north, leaving behind\"}, {\"start\": 219.32, \"end\": 227.74, \"text\": \"violence and poverty in Central America.\"}, {\"start\": 227.74, \"end\": 235.22, \"text\": \"Organizers say the annual pilgrimage usually starts with more than 1,000 people.\"}, {\"start\": 235.22, \"end\": 241.38, \"text\": \"Most of the people didn’t even know each other two weeks ago.\"}, {\"start\": 241.38, \"end\": 248.0, \"text\": \"But the group becomes smaller as it heads north.\"}, {\"start\": 248.08, \"end\": 254.58, \"text\": \"Some plan to stay in Mexico, some plan to break off on their own, while others will\"}, {\"start\": 254.66, \"end\": 258.48, \"text\": \"continue the arduous journey north to the US border.\"}, {\"start\": 258.48, \"end\": 264.38, \"text\": \"Only about half of them will make it to the US/Mexico border.\"}, {\"start\": 264.38, \"end\": 270.12, \"text\": \"President Trump has bashed the caravan, calling them “dangerous.”\"}, {\"start\": 270.2, \"end\": 277.94, \"text\": \"But many say Trump doesn’t understand what their journey is all about.\"}, {\"start\": 278.02, \"end\": 283.08, \"text\": \"For them this is about a search for a better life.\"}, {\"start\": 283.08, \"end\": 289.76, \"text\": \"One woman said: “If Jesus had to migrate, why shouldn’t we.”\"}, {\"start\": 292.86, \"end\": 303.66, \"text\": \"An investigation is underway into a deadly fire at Trump Tower in New York.\"}, {\"start\": 303.66, \"end\": 310.0, \"text\": \"The fire broke out at around 7 PM last night on the 50th floor.\"}, {\"start\": 310.0, \"end\": 313.44, \"text\": \"Two hundred firefighters responded on the scene.\"}, {\"start\": 313.44, \"end\": 318.62, \"text\": \"Rescuers found one resident unconscious and unresponsive.\"}, {\"start\": 318.62, \"end\": 325.08, \"text\": \"He was rushed to a local hospital in critical condition but later died.\"}, {\"start\": 325.08, \"end\": 331.74, \"text\": \"Six firefighters were hurt but none of their injuries were life-threatening.\"}, {\"start\": 331.74, \"end\": 337.7, \"text\": \"President Trump has an apartment in the building but none of his family members were there\"}, {\"start\": 337.78, \"end\": 341.66, \"text\": \"and there was only minor smoke damage to the President’s resident.\"}, {\"start\": 344.38, \"end\": 355.28, \"text\": \"Aalayah Eastmond, one of the Parkland school shooting survivors, is organizing an anti-gun\"}, {\"start\": 355.28, \"end\": 358.98, \"text\": \"violence March in New York.\"}, {\"start\": 358.98, \"end\": 366.28, \"text\": \"She says the youth march against gun violence will get underway on June 2.\"}, {\"start\": 366.28, \"end\": 370.92, \"text\": \"The high school junior made the announcement alongside civil rights activist Al Sharpton\"}, {\"start\": 370.92, \"end\": 372.52, \"text\": \"on Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 372.52, \"end\": 378.22, \"text\": \"Eastmond said she survived the shooting by taking cover under the body of one of her\"}, {\"start\": 378.36, \"end\": 380.82, \"text\": \"dead classmates.\"}, {\"start\": 380.82, \"end\": 388.1, \"text\": \"Because of that experience, she says she has to speak up.\"}, {\"start\": 388.1, \"end\": 393.7, \"text\": \"Eastmond also says she will march to speak up against gun violence affecting the black\"}, {\"start\": 393.7, \"end\": 395.72, \"text\": \"community.\"}, {\"start\": 398.74, \"end\": 410.1, \"text\": \"Agents from the Tennessee Bureau of Investigation arrested Joseph Ray Daniels Saturday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 410.1, \"end\": 416.46, \"text\": \"He’s the father of Joe Clyde Daniels, the five-year-old autistic boy that has been missing\"}, {\"start\": 416.46, \"end\": 420.16, \"text\": \"for three days.\"}, {\"start\": 420.16, \"end\": 426.1, \"text\": \"Investigators say Daniels confessed to intentionally killing his son sometime before Wednesday\"}, {\"start\": 426.1, \"end\": 430.5, \"text\": \"morning in their home and then hid his body.\"}, {\"start\": 430.5, \"end\": 436.12, \"text\": \"Despite an extensive search by law enforcement, rescue organizations and volunteers, the child’s\"}, {\"start\": 436.12, \"end\": 437.98, \"text\": \"body has not been found.\"}, {\"start\": 437.98, \"end\": 442.78, \"text\": \"But now that the father has confessed, they hope to make a discovery soon.\"}, {\"start\": 442.78, \"end\": 454.3, \"text\": \"Daniels is charged with one count of criminal homicide and is being held in jail on a $1\"}, {\"start\": 454.3, \"end\": 456.46, \"text\": \"million bond.\"}, {\"start\": 458.06, \"end\": 462.46, \"text\": \"Here’s a quick recap of the big winners at this weekend’s box office.\"}, {\"start\": 462.46, \"end\": 466.74, \"text\": \"“A Quiet Place” takes the top spot.\"}, {\"start\": 466.74, \"end\": 474.22, \"text\": \"The thriller stars Deaf actress Millicent Simmonds.\"}, {\"start\": 474.22, \"end\": 477.08, \"text\": \"She also starred in the movie “Wonderstruck.”\"}, {\"start\": 477.08, \"end\": 483.08, \"text\": \"It brought in $50.3 million in its opening weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 483.08, \"end\": 493.82, \"text\": \"According to Variety.com, that’s the second highest domestic opening of the year behind\"}, {\"start\": 493.82, \"end\": 496.56, \"text\": \"“Black Panther.”\"}, {\"start\": 496.56, \"end\": 507.42, \"text\": \"In the number two spot at the box office Steven Spielberg’s “Ready Player One.”\"}, {\"start\": 507.42, \"end\": 510.78, \"text\": \"It brought in $25 million.\"}, {\"start\": 510.78, \"end\": 520.18, \"text\": \"And rounding out the top three “Blockers,” the R-rated comedy made $21.4 million.\"}, {\"start\": 522.88, \"end\": 526.24, \"text\": \"Listen up all of you pet lovers!\"}, {\"start\": 526.24, \"end\": 531.14, \"text\": \"This Wednesday, April 11, is National Pet Day.\"}, {\"start\": 531.14, \"end\": 539.04, \"text\": \"The day is designed to share love with those pets who don’t have anyone by volunteering\"}, {\"start\": 539.14, \"end\": 545.28, \"text\": \"at, donating to or adopting from a local shelter.\"}, {\"start\": 545.28, \"end\": 547.56, \"text\": \"It’s also a day to show how much you love your furry or feathered friends by throwing\"}, {\"start\": 547.56, \"end\": 558.12, \"text\": \"a pet day party, buying a new pet toy or sharing photos on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 558.18, \"end\": 561.58, \"text\": \"Like this.\"}, {\"start\": 561.58, \"end\": 565.2, \"text\": \"This is a love of my life –Jahlan.\"}, {\"start\": 565.2, \"end\": 568.72, \"text\": \"I can’t imagine my life without him.\"}, {\"start\": 568.72, \"end\": 577.36, \"text\": \"So head to our Facebook page and send us the cutest, silliest, most precious photos of\"}, {\"start\": 577.4, \"end\": 583.34, \"text\": \"you and your pets and we will share them during our broadcast this Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 583.34, \"end\": 586.34, \"text\": \"We can’t wait to see your pictures!\"}, {\"start\": 590.42, \"end\": 592.86, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 592.98, \"end\": 594.52, \"text\": \"I’m Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 594.52, \"end\": 596.48, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 596.48, \"end\": 600.6, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 600.6, \"end\": 602.04, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 602.04, \"end\": 603.38, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 603.38, \"end\": 606.62, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "xHT55ZYj4cI": {
    "video_id": "xHT55ZYj4cI",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.1.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180102",
    "duration": 595,
    "view_count": 4000,
    "description": "1.1.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-New details in deadly Colorado shooting\n-New York family of 5 killed in Costa Rica crash\n-Death toll rises in nationwide Iran protests\n-Kim Jong Un has a nuclear button on his desk\n-US military to accept transgender recruits\n-Minimum wage hikes kick in for 18 states\n-New Year's Eve fireworks around the world\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.28, \"end\": 9.32, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.32, \"end\": 10.86, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.86, \"end\": 12.14, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.14, \"end\": 14.58, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.18, \"end\": 23.76, \"text\": \"New details are emerging about the deadly shooting at a Colorado apartment complex yesterday.\"}, {\"start\": 23.76, \"end\": 32.72, \"text\": \"Police say the suspect, 37-year-old Matthew Riehl, conducted an ambush-style attack on\"}, {\"start\": 32.72, \"end\": 34.72, \"text\": \"the officers.\"}, {\"start\": 34.72, \"end\": 38.34, \"text\": \"He knew they were coming.\"}, {\"start\": 38.34, \"end\": 44.24, \"text\": \"Deputies were twice called to the apartment where Riehl was inside.\"}, {\"start\": 44.24, \"end\": 57.94, \"text\": \"First for a noise complaint, then for a domestic disturbance report.\"}, {\"start\": 57.96, \"end\": 63.18, \"text\": \"On the second call, several deputies arrived at the scene and entered the apartment.\"}, {\"start\": 63.18, \"end\": 78.24, \"text\": \"Authorities say Riehl barricaded himself in a bedroom and then suddenly opened fire with\"}, {\"start\": 78.24, \"end\": 82.7, \"text\": \"a rifle, firing over 100 rounds.\"}, {\"start\": 82.7, \"end\": 91.16, \"text\": \"29-year-old deputy Zackari Parrish was killed.\"}, {\"start\": 91.16, \"end\": 93.64, \"text\": \"Four other deputies were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 93.64, \"end\": 104.58, \"text\": \"Riehl was killed about 90 minutes later when a tactical team entered the apartment.\"}, {\"start\": 104.58, \"end\": 121.78, \"text\": \"Police officers formed a caravan to accompany Parrish's coffin to the corner's office.\"}, {\"start\": 121.78, \"end\": 126.7, \"text\": \"Citizens lined the street to show their respect.\"}, {\"start\": 126.7, \"end\": 137.0, \"text\": \"And memorials have sprung up, started by local people compelled to show their sorrow and\"}, {\"start\": 137.0, \"end\": 140.32, \"text\": \"their support.\"}, {\"start\": 143.48, \"end\": 151.6, \"text\": \"An investigation is underway in Costa Rica to determine the cause of a plane crash.\"}, {\"start\": 151.6, \"end\": 156.9, \"text\": \"The single-engine plane went down on New Year's Eve.\"}, {\"start\": 156.9, \"end\": 162.76, \"text\": \"The crash happened 10 minutes after takeoff from the airport after heavy winds reportedly\"}, {\"start\": 162.8, \"end\": 170.28, \"text\": \"forced the pilots to change course and land at a different airport.\"}, {\"start\": 170.28, \"end\": 179.12, \"text\": \"Everyone on board was killed -- 10 Americans and two pilots.\"}, {\"start\": 179.18, \"end\": 183.88, \"text\": \"Five of those killed were members of the same family.\"}, {\"start\": 183.88, \"end\": 206.34, \"text\": \"Bruce and Irene Steinberg, along with their three children, Zachary, William and Matthew.\"}, {\"start\": 209.04, \"end\": 218.58, \"text\": \"Today marks day five of anti-government protests across Iran.\"}, {\"start\": 218.58, \"end\": 225.16, \"text\": \"This is being called the largest public display of outrage in nearly a decade.\"}, {\"start\": 225.16, \"end\": 232.1, \"text\": \"Twelve people have been killed in nationwide protests that began Thursday.\"}, {\"start\": 232.1, \"end\": 243.96, \"text\": \"People are voicing their outrage over corruption and raising food and gas prices.\"}, {\"start\": 244.02, \"end\": 252.06, \"text\": \"Iran's president said people are free to express their feelings but warns protesters violence\"}, {\"start\": 252.06, \"end\": 259.0, \"text\": \"will not be tolerated and they will \\\"pay the price.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 261.66, \"end\": 274.24, \"text\": \"North Korean leader Kim Jong Un warned the United States that the nuclear button is always\"}, {\"start\": 274.24, \"end\": 278.54, \"text\": \"on his desk.\"}, {\"start\": 278.54, \"end\": 286.98, \"text\": \"In his New Year's address to his country, he said \\\"the entire mainland of the US is\"}, {\"start\": 286.98, \"end\": 290.48, \"text\": \"within the range of our nuclear weapons and the nuclear button is always on the desk of\"}, {\"start\": 290.48, \"end\": 292.96, \"text\": \"my office.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 292.96, \"end\": 300.68, \"text\": \"\\\"They should actually be aware that this is not a threat but a reality.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 300.68, \"end\": 309.68, \"text\": \"He also declared that his country is a \\\"responsible nuclear nation and loves peace\\\" and said that\"}, {\"start\": 309.68, \"end\": 315.94, \"text\": \"as long as there is no aggression directed at North Korea \\\"we do not intend to use nuclear\"}, {\"start\": 315.94, \"end\": 317.62, \"text\": \"powers.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 317.62, \"end\": 326.0, \"text\": \"But despite those declarations, Kim then call for accelerated production of nuclear warheads\"}, {\"start\": 326.02, \"end\": 329.1, \"text\": \"and ballistic missiles.\"}, {\"start\": 331.66, \"end\": 339.06, \"text\": \"The new year brings new hope for transgender individuals who want to join the military.\"}, {\"start\": 339.06, \"end\": 343.86, \"text\": \"The Defense Department is taking steps to receive transgender recruits into the ranks\"}, {\"start\": 343.86, \"end\": 346.2, \"text\": \"as soon as today.\"}, {\"start\": 346.2, \"end\": 353.5, \"text\": \"But those who join know the legal road ahead could be bumpy.\"}, {\"start\": 353.5, \"end\": 363.14, \"text\": \"President Trump announced a transgender ban in August but it is yet to be implemented.\"}, {\"start\": 363.14, \"end\": 373.38, \"text\": \"Last month a second federal judge blocked enforcement of the prohibition.\"}, {\"start\": 376.64, \"end\": 384.48, \"text\": \"The start of the new year means bigger paychecks for some workers across the US.\"}, {\"start\": 384.48, \"end\": 393.62, \"text\": \"Minimum hourly wages are up in 18 states along, with a handful of other cities and counties.\"}, {\"start\": 393.62, \"end\": 402.24, \"text\": \"In Washington State the minimum wage jumped $.50 to $11.50 an hour.\"}, {\"start\": 402.24, \"end\": 412.86, \"text\": \"The biggest per hour jump is $1 in Maine from $9 to $10.\"}, {\"start\": 412.86, \"end\": 421.56, \"text\": \"The highest local minimum wage is found in SeaTac in Washington State -- $15.64 an hour,\"}, {\"start\": 421.56, \"end\": 426.26, \"text\": \"while Seattle is $15.45 an hour.\"}, {\"start\": 426.3, \"end\": 433.0, \"text\": \"There are a number of California cities now with minimums at $13 an hour or more.\"}, {\"start\": 433.0, \"end\": 445.86, \"text\": \"Many of the wage bumps come as a result of ballot measures with backing from union and\"}, {\"start\": 445.86, \"end\": 451.4, \"text\": \"workers rights groups.\"}, {\"start\": 451.4, \"end\": 455.96, \"text\": \"A number of the hikes are scheduled to continue to rise in the coming years.\"}, {\"start\": 455.96, \"end\": 462.56, \"text\": \"The federal minimum wage currently stands at $7.25 an hour.\"}, {\"start\": 462.56, \"end\": 468.8, \"text\": \"If you want to see the full list of the 18 states, go to money.cnn.com.\"}, {\"start\": 472.0, \"end\": 479.04, \"text\": \"We hope everyone had a wonderful and safe New Year's Eve.\"}, {\"start\": 479.04, \"end\": 483.58, \"text\": \"If you couldn't get out to enjoy the fireworks, don't worry.\"}, {\"start\": 483.58, \"end\": 485.76, \"text\": \"We're bringing the fireworks to you!\"}, {\"start\": 485.76, \"end\": 491.42, \"text\": \"Here's a montage of fireworks celebrations from all over the world: New York, London,\"}, {\"start\": 491.42, \"end\": 497.72, \"text\": \"Paris, Australia, Berlin and Hong Kong.\"}, {\"start\": 497.76, \"end\": 500.48, \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"}, {\"start\": 571.36, \"end\": 573.46, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 573.46, \"end\": 574.82, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 574.82, \"end\": 576.88, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 576.88, \"end\": 581.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 581.0, \"end\": 587.12, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "n7u6UW8CuPo": {
    "video_id": "n7u6UW8CuPo",
    "title": "Powerball and Mega-Millions Jackpots over $300M (ASL 12.28.17)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171229",
    "duration": 63,
    "view_count": 136,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.64, \"end\": 8.48, \"text\": \"If you're feeling lucky, you may want to buy a lottery ticket this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 8.48, \"end\": 18.88, \"text\": \"The Megamillions jackpot is now at $306 million and growing.\"}, {\"start\": 18.88, \"end\": 25.12, \"text\": \"The next drawing is 11 PM Eastern time on Friday night.\"}, {\"start\": 25.12, \"end\": 36.5, \"text\": \"And the Powerball jackpot has jumped to $384 million after no winners in Wednesday night's drawing.\"}, {\"start\": 36.5, \"end\": 41.98, \"text\": \"A ticket worth $2 million was sold in Georgia.\"}, {\"start\": 41.98, \"end\": 54.9, \"text\": \"The odds of winning the Powerball drawing 1 in 292.2 million.\"}, {\"start\": 54.9, \"end\": 60.18, \"text\": \"The next Powerball drawing is Saturday night.\"}, {\"start\": 60.18, \"end\": 62.06, \"text\": \"Good luck!\"}]"
  },
  "G5mm813Au1A": {
    "video_id": "G5mm813Au1A",
    "title": "Protests over Trump visit to Davos (ASL - 1.24.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180125",
    "duration": 76,
    "view_count": 166,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.12, \"end\": 17.42, \"text\": \"President Trump is taking his \\\"America First\\\" message to the world economic forum in Davos,\"}, {\"start\": 17.42, \"end\": 18.48, \"text\": \"Switzerland this week.\"}, {\"start\": 18.48, \"end\": 33.32, \"text\": \"However thousands of people marched through Zurich and other major Swiss cities to demonstrate\"}, {\"start\": 33.32, \"end\": 36.56, \"text\": \"against Trump's visit.\"}, {\"start\": 36.56, \"end\": 46.12, \"text\": \"Leaders from France, Germany and Italy will address the forum Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 46.16, \"end\": 50.28, \"text\": \"And Trump will give his keynote address on Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 50.28, \"end\": 61.52, \"text\": \"The forum brings together leaders from all over the world to discuss free-trade and international\"}, {\"start\": 61.52, \"end\": 63.32, \"text\": \"cooperation.\"}, {\"start\": 63.32, \"end\": 75.44, \"text\": \"President Trump is the first US president to attend the summit in almost 20 years.\"}]"
  },
  "RRd2DlRgibg": {
    "video_id": "RRd2DlRgibg",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.20.20",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200421",
    "duration": 818,
    "view_count": 552,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n\n- More protests erupt over stay-at-home orders \n- Experts say grocery stores may need to ban customers \n- Small business package deal expected Monday, Shake Shack returns $10M\n- Dogs being trained to sniff out coronavirus\n- Sign1News anchor wins Battle of the Hammock: Round 2!",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.36, \"end\": 10.84, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 10.84, \"end\": 16.2, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 16.2, \"end\": 19.38, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 19.38, \"end\": 26.72, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 28.88, \"end\": 40.88, \"text\": \"This weekend more protests erupted calling for an end to stay-at-home orders as protesters\"}, {\"start\": 40.88, \"end\": 45.68, \"text\": \"ignored social distancing guidelines.\"}, {\"start\": 45.68, \"end\": 56.96, \"text\": \"In recent days, Michigan, Ohio, Kentucky, Minnesota, North Carolina, Utah, Colorado\"}, {\"start\": 56.96, \"end\": 62.16, \"text\": \"and Washington state have all seen protests.\"}, {\"start\": 62.16, \"end\": 74.08, \"text\": \"Over the weekend car horns blared in the streets in Annapolis, Maryland as members of the group\"}, {\"start\": 74.08, \"end\": 81.52, \"text\": \"\\\"ReOpen\\\" protested, saying the closures have been financially devastating.\"}, {\"start\": 81.52, \"end\": 90.52, \"text\": \"Maryland's Republican governor responded that he understands the frustration of the people\"}, {\"start\": 90.52, \"end\": 98.74, \"text\": \"that want to get things reopened right away and that he is frustrated also.\"}, {\"start\": 98.74, \"end\": 106.78, \"text\": \"But he said he doesn't think it's helpful to encourage demonstrations.\"}, {\"start\": 106.78, \"end\": 114.44, \"text\": \"More protests are expected on Monday including in western New York state.\"}, {\"start\": 114.44, \"end\": 128.74, \"text\": \"Some health officials and governors say a lot more testing is needed before restrictions are eased.\"}, {\"start\": 128.74, \"end\": 136.28, \"text\": \"According to data from Johns Hopkins University, as of Monday morning,\"}, {\"start\": 136.28, \"end\": 149.04, \"text\": \"the US has reported over 759-thousand coronavirus cases and 40-thousand deaths.\"}, {\"start\": 149.04, \"end\": 164.88, \"text\": \"Dozens of grocery store workers have died from coronavirus, despite masks, temperature\"}, {\"start\": 164.88, \"end\": 176.26, \"text\": \"checks and capacity restrictions to keep them safe.\"}, {\"start\": 176.26, \"end\": 190.04, \"text\": \"Worker experts, union leaders and small grocery owners believe it has become too dangerous\"}, {\"start\": 190.04, \"end\": 198.6, \"text\": \"to let customers grocery shop in stores due to the pandemic.\"}, {\"start\": 198.6, \"end\": 211.08, \"text\": \"Experts say it's time for large chains to close its doors to the public and convert\"}, {\"start\": 211.08, \"end\": 223.8, \"text\": \"to curbside pickup and home delivery for food and other essential goods.\"}, {\"start\": 223.8, \"end\": 243.22, \"text\": \"According to the president of the United Food and Commercial Workers Union \\\"careless customers\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 243.22, \"end\": 246.84, \"text\": \"are \\\"probably the biggest threat\\\" to workers right now.\"}, {\"start\": 246.84, \"end\": 256.86, \"text\": \"The union said 85% of its grocery store member workers reported that customers are not practicing\"}, {\"start\": 256.88, \"end\": 263.52, \"text\": \"social distancing in stores.\"}, {\"start\": 263.52, \"end\": 276.96, \"text\": \"Many small, independent grocery stores have moved to pickup and delivery only to protect their staff.\"}, {\"start\": 276.96, \"end\": 289.78, \"text\": \"Some large companies like Best Buy have also switched to this model during the crisis.\"}, {\"start\": 297.38, \"end\": 317.48, \"text\": \"Congress is hoping to agree on $300 billion of additional money for the paycheck protection\"}, {\"start\": 317.48, \"end\": 323.04, \"text\": \"program, which is designed to provide loans to businesses shuttered by coronavirus restrictions.\"}, {\"start\": 323.04, \"end\": 335.38, \"text\": \"The government's small business relief program could be decided Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 335.38, \"end\": 346.16, \"text\": \"However there has been growing backlash over how the funds have been distributed.\"}, {\"start\": 346.16, \"end\": 360.8, \"text\": \"The programs initial $349 billion allocation was exhausted in a few weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 360.8, \"end\": 374.78, \"text\": \"And many small business owners faced rejection while larger establishments like Shake Shack\"}, {\"start\": 374.78, \"end\": 382.94, \"text\": \"and Potbelly Sandwich shop landed multimillion-dollar loans.\"}, {\"start\": 382.94, \"end\": 392.7, \"text\": \"On Monday Shake Shack announced it will return the ten-million dollar loan it received from\"}, {\"start\": 392.7, \"end\": 394.92, \"text\": \"the government.\"}, {\"start\": 394.92, \"end\": 406.72, \"text\": \"The CEO of the company said it would benefit from the financial boost but isn't keeping\"}, {\"start\": 406.72, \"end\": 413.62, \"text\": \"the funds because it has \\\"access to capital that others do not.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 413.62, \"end\": 425.44, \"text\": \"The small business funding bill is also expected to include 75 billion dollars for hospitals\"}, {\"start\": 425.44, \"end\": 429.16, \"text\": \"and 25 billion for coronavirus testing.\"}, {\"start\": 429.16, \"end\": 437.3, \"text\": \"It is not expected to include money for state and local governments with budgets crippled\"}, {\"start\": 437.3, \"end\": 439.44, \"text\": \"by the current crisis.\"}, {\"start\": 444.92, \"end\": 461.72, \"text\": \"Canines have been used for decades to sniff out drugs, bombs, dead bodies and even cancer.\"}, {\"start\": 461.72, \"end\": 484.46, \"text\": \"Now a team of British researchers are training dogs to see if they can sniff out coronavirus\"}, {\"start\": 484.46, \"end\": 505.2, \"text\": \"in people, including those who don't have any symptoms.\"}, {\"start\": 505.2, \"end\": 514.72, \"text\": \"The London School of Hygiene and Tropical Medicine recently discovered canines can detect\"}, {\"start\": 514.72, \"end\": 528.02, \"text\": \"malaria infections in humans and they are investigating whether the same is true for\"}, {\"start\": 528.02, \"end\": 531.96, \"text\": \"COVID-19.\"}, {\"start\": 531.96, \"end\": 543.5, \"text\": \"The training began in March and researchers are eyeing six weeks as enough time to determine\"}, {\"start\": 543.5, \"end\": 549.34, \"text\": \"if the dogs can sniff out the virus.\"}, {\"start\": 549.34, \"end\": 564.16, \"text\": \"If so, these dogs could be deployed to screen up to 250 people per hour.\"}, {\"start\": 564.16, \"end\": 575.26, \"text\": \"They caution it won't replace traditional testing but rather be used as a supplement\"}, {\"start\": 575.26, \"end\": 595.68, \"text\": \"since COVID-19 tests are in short supply and often take hours or days for results to come back.\"}, {\"start\": 595.68, \"end\": 609.6, \"text\": \"The dogs could be used at airports or other public areas to help prevent another outbreak\"}, {\"start\": 609.6, \"end\": 613.26, \"text\": \"once the current epidemic declines.\"}, {\"start\": 615.92, \"end\": 631.3, \"text\": \"A few weeks ago Sign1News anchor Jethro Wooddall's attempt to set up a hammock in his yard ended badly.\"}, {\"start\": 631.3, \"end\": 642.54, \"text\": \"One of the 4 x 4 wooden stakes he put in the ground snapped\"}, {\"start\": 642.54, \"end\": 649.98, \"text\": \"and whacked him across the back of the head so hard, it left a knot the size of a softball.\"}, {\"start\": 649.98, \"end\": 655.3, \"text\": \"If you haven't seen the video, it's definitely worth watching.\"}, {\"start\": 655.3, \"end\": 664.46, \"text\": \"But at the end of that video, Jethro promised there would be a \\\"Battle of Hammock: Round\"}, {\"start\": 664.46, \"end\": 667.12, \"text\": \"Two\\\" and he would win this time.\"}, {\"start\": 667.12, \"end\": 668.66, \"text\": \"And guess what?\"}, {\"start\": 668.66, \"end\": 672.22, \"text\": \"He did.\"}, {\"start\": 727.28, \"end\": 731.46, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 731.46, \"end\": 733.74, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 733.74, \"end\": 737.3, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 737.3, \"end\": 746.08, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our\"}, {\"start\": 746.08, \"end\": 749.32, \"text\": \"app too.\"}, {\"start\": 749.32, \"end\": 755.76, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "wldGPG8Me_M": {
    "video_id": "wldGPG8Me_M",
    "title": "Cruise control designs could solve traffic jams (ASL - Sign1News - 12.16.17)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171217",
    "duration": 72,
    "view_count": 209,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.38, \"end\": 11.7, \"text\": \"MIT researchers believe they have found a new way to stop frustrating \\\"stop-and-go\\\" traffic.\"}, {\"start\": 11.78, \"end\": 21.44, \"text\": \"Researchers published a paper this week offering\"}, {\"start\": 21.44, \"end\": 32.16, \"text\": \"cruise control as a solution to help alleviate traffic jams.\"}, {\"start\": 32.16, \"end\": 39.46, \"text\": \"The report proposes redesigning the cruise control feature on cars to factor\"}, {\"start\": 39.52, \"end\": 43.32, \"text\": \"in the space in front and behind the vehicle.\"}, {\"start\": 43.32, \"end\": 49.38, \"text\": \"Simulations showed that keeping the same distance between the vehicle\"}, {\"start\": 49.38, \"end\": 54.4, \"text\": \"in the front and the vehicle in the back prevents traffic jams.\"}, {\"start\": 54.44, \"end\": 57.32, \"text\": \"But there is a catch.\"}, {\"start\": 57.32, \"end\": 61.46, \"text\": \"In order for the redesigned cruise control to work and have an immediate impact on traffic\"}, {\"start\": 61.5, \"end\": 71.16, \"text\": \"lots of drivers have to use the technology.\"}]"
  },
  "fblxrnHHYL4": {
    "video_id": "fblxrnHHYL4",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.22.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180223",
    "duration": 635,
    "view_count": 1618,
    "description": "2.22.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Trump goes on twitter tirade\n-NRA responds to criticism during CPAC convention\n-Syria’s horror and future of its children\n-Space-X PAZ mission launch\n-Uber introduces cheaper “Express Pool”\n-Avocado proposals \n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal acc",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.3, \"end\": 7.56, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.56, \"end\": 9.48, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.48, \"end\": 11.0, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.0, \"end\": 14.32, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.44, \"end\": 26.96, \"text\": \"President Trump spent the past 24 hours tweeting furiously in response to comments and criticisms\"}, {\"start\": 26.96, \"end\": 37.48, \"text\": \"involving the Parkland, Florida shooting, gun sale background checks and the NRA.\"}, {\"start\": 37.48, \"end\": 46.12, \"text\": \"The first tweet is in response to comments he made during his listening session yesterday\"}, {\"start\": 46.12, \"end\": 55.04, \"text\": \"with survivors of gun violence in which he suggested arming teachers with guns.\"}, {\"start\": 55.04, \"end\": 65.66, \"text\": \"He tweeted: \\\"I never said 'give teacher's guns' like was stated on fake news @CNN and @NBC.\"}, {\"start\": 65.66, \"end\": 73.8, \"text\": \"What I said was to look at the possibility of giving 'concealed guns to gun teachers\"}, {\"start\": 73.8, \"end\": 81.46, \"text\": \"with military or special training experience, only the best.\"}, {\"start\": 81.46, \"end\": 91.2, \"text\": \"20% of teachers, a lot, would now be able to immediately fire back if a savage sicko\"}, {\"start\": 91.2, \"end\": 94.92, \"text\": \"came to a school with bad intentions.\"}, {\"start\": 94.92, \"end\": 102.72, \"text\": \"Highly trained teachers would also serve as a deterrent to the cowards that do this.\"}, {\"start\": 102.72, \"end\": 109.84, \"text\": \"Far more assets at much less cost than guards.\"}, {\"start\": 109.84, \"end\": 115.9, \"text\": \"A 'gun free' school is a magnet for bad people.\"}, {\"start\": 115.9, \"end\": 120.5, \"text\": \"Attacks would end!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 120.5, \"end\": 129.86, \"text\": \"He later addressed background checks by tweeting\\\" \\\"I will be strongly pushing Comprehensive\"}, {\"start\": 129.86, \"end\": 135.19, \"text\": \"Background Checks with an emphasis on mental health.\"}, {\"start\": 135.19, \"end\": 149.06, \"text\": \"Raise age to 21 and end sale of Bump Stocks!\"}, {\"start\": 149.06, \"end\": 157.38, \"text\": \"Congress is in a mood to finally do something on this issue, I hope!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 157.46, \"end\": 166.72, \"text\": \"Many people have been critical of the National Rifle Association's (NRA) resistance to certain\"}, {\"start\": 166.72, \"end\": 172.98, \"text\": \"gun limitations, specifically the AR-15.\"}, {\"start\": 172.98, \"end\": 182.22, \"text\": \"This was Trump's response\\\" 'What many people don't understand, or don't want to understand,\"}, {\"start\": 182.22, \"end\": 192.2, \"text\": \"is that Wayne, Chris and the folks who work so hard at the NRA are great people and great\"}, {\"start\": 192.2, \"end\": 195.6, \"text\": \"American patriots.\"}, {\"start\": 195.6, \"end\": 199.96, \"text\": \"They love our country and will do the right thing.\"}, {\"start\": 199.96, \"end\": 203.38, \"text\": \"Make America great again!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 206.32, \"end\": 216.56, \"text\": \"The NRA is a longtime sponsor of the Conservative Political Action Conference (CPAC).\"}, {\"start\": 216.68, \"end\": 229.14, \"text\": \"NRA CEO Wayne LaPierre and several NRA spokespersons\"}, {\"start\": 229.14, \"end\": 232.54, \"text\": \"were keynote speakers at the conference today.\"}, {\"start\": 232.54, \"end\": 242.0, \"text\": \"LaPierre accused Democrats of exploiting the Florida tragedy for political gain, that they\"}, {\"start\": 242.0, \"end\": 247.98, \"text\": \"care more about control and eliminating the Second Amendment than they do about school\"}, {\"start\": 247.98, \"end\": 250.44, \"text\": \"children.\"}, {\"start\": 250.44, \"end\": 262.68, \"text\": \"NRA spokesperson Dana Loesch said the NRA is not responsible for the tragedy in Florida\"}, {\"start\": 262.68, \"end\": 270.78, \"text\": \"and accused the media of loving the mass shootings because it increases ratings.\"}, {\"start\": 270.78, \"end\": 283.4, \"text\": \"She said crying white mothers are \\\"ratings gold\\\" for the media.\"}, {\"start\": 285.78, \"end\": 295.12, \"text\": \"We want to warn you: some of the video you'll see in this story will be graphic.\"}, {\"start\": 295.12, \"end\": 300.22, \"text\": \"There appears to be no end in sight for the bloodshed going on in Syria's Eastern Ghouta\"}, {\"start\": 300.22, \"end\": 301.34, \"text\": \"right now.\"}, {\"start\": 301.34, \"end\": 308.539, \"text\": \"There have been three days of relentless bombing.\"}, {\"start\": 308.54, \"end\": 319.78, \"text\": \"The carnage unleashed by Syria's own president against rebel fighters.\"}, {\"start\": 319.78, \"end\": 326.0, \"text\": \"The death toll is close to 100 a day.\"}, {\"start\": 326.0, \"end\": 330.64, \"text\": \"Sadly, many of the victims are children.\"}, {\"start\": 330.66, \"end\": 341.34, \"text\": \"Children who have lost their parents to war now live underground, living with rats.\"}, {\"start\": 341.34, \"end\": 347.22, \"text\": \"Even the newly born are taken beneath the earth.\"}, {\"start\": 347.22, \"end\": 352.78, \"text\": \"And the conditions there are brutal.\"}, {\"start\": 352.78, \"end\": 359.76, \"text\": \"The cold is killing the children.\"}, {\"start\": 359.76, \"end\": 368.32, \"text\": \"There are only eight incubators and one intensive care room.\"}, {\"start\": 368.32, \"end\": 376.52, \"text\": \"Medical supplies are so rare the staff have resorted to recycling medicine and syringes.\"}, {\"start\": 376.52, \"end\": 382.74, \"text\": \"Meanwhile the Syrian government has pledged to destroy the rebels, promising to teach\"}, {\"start\": 382.74, \"end\": 391.14, \"text\": \"them a lesson in combat and in fire and there will be no one to rescue them -- words that\"}, {\"start\": 391.14, \"end\": 398.18, \"text\": \"may haunt the children for the rest of their lives.\"}, {\"start\": 400.26, \"end\": 413.3, \"text\": \"A Space-X Falcon 9 rocket launched Thursday morning from California's Vandenberg Air Force Base.\"}, {\"start\": 413.3, \"end\": 424.56, \"text\": \"The primary mission is to deliver Spain's Paz satellite into low orbit.\"}, {\"start\": 424.56, \"end\": 431.56, \"text\": \"But the rocket also gets founder Elon Musk closer to his goal of providing high-speed\"}, {\"start\": 431.56, \"end\": 439.68, \"text\": \"internet to the world using thousands of tiny satellites.\"}, {\"start\": 439.68, \"end\": 448.479, \"text\": \"Along with the Paz satellite, the Falcon 9 rocket carried two experimental internet delivery\"}, {\"start\": 448.48, \"end\": 450.5, \"text\": \"satellites.\"}, {\"start\": 450.5, \"end\": 467.36, \"text\": \"Space-X will use them to test technology designed to beam high-speed internet to Earth's surface.\"}, {\"start\": 469.84, \"end\": 487.0, \"text\": \"On Wednesday ridesharing company Uber announced a new service called \\\"Express Pool.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 487.04, \"end\": 488.54, \"text\": \"Here's how it works:\"}, {\"start\": 488.54, \"end\": 495.68, \"text\": \"Uber customers requesting express pool rides are paired with other nearby riders heading\"}, {\"start\": 495.68, \"end\": 498.08, \"text\": \"to destinations close to each other.\"}, {\"start\": 498.08, \"end\": 506.24, \"text\": \"They then have to walk to a location no further than two blocks away to meet their car, which\"}, {\"start\": 506.24, \"end\": 509.76, \"text\": \"is shared with other riders.\"}, {\"start\": 509.76, \"end\": 516.16, \"text\": \"The driver drops them off near, but not necessarily exactly at, their final destinations.\"}, {\"start\": 516.16, \"end\": 525.44, \"text\": \"Uber says fares for express pool could be up to 75% lower than its Uber-X service, but\"}, {\"start\": 525.44, \"end\": 532.8, \"text\": \"the price to ride is still subject to surge pricing.\"}, {\"start\": 532.8, \"end\": 546.8, \"text\": \"Uber express pool will launch in Washington DC, Los Angeles, Miami, Philadelphia and Denver.\"}, {\"start\": 546.8, \"end\": 554.72, \"text\": \"However it has been testing in San Francisco and Boston since last year.\"}, {\"start\": 556.28, \"end\": 562.82, \"text\": \"Everyone knows avocados are tasty and good for you.\"}, {\"start\": 562.82, \"end\": 571.42, \"text\": \"But who knew they were a great place to hide engagement rings?\"}, {\"start\": 571.42, \"end\": 579.12, \"text\": \"Yep, there's a growing trend among young people on social media surprising their loved ones\"}, {\"start\": 579.16, \"end\": 584.18, \"text\": \"with rings inside avocados.\"}, {\"start\": 584.18, \"end\": 594.2, \"text\": \"A few weeks ago, a cookbook author posted a picture of the \\\"Avo-Box\\\" and wrote \\\"tag\"}, {\"start\": 594.2, \"end\": 598.06, \"text\": \"someone who should propose like this.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 598.06, \"end\": 601.66, \"text\": \"Thousands of people did.\"}, {\"start\": 601.66, \"end\": 609.18, \"text\": \"There's even a hashtag -- #avocadoproposal.\"}, {\"start\": 610.38, \"end\": 612.68, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 612.68, \"end\": 614.4, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 614.4, \"end\": 616.48, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 616.48, \"end\": 620.9, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 620.9, \"end\": 627.26, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-hPALuvcMsM": {
    "video_id": "-hPALuvcMsM",
    "title": "October 3, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171004",
    "duration": 560,
    "view_count": 166,
    "description": "October 3, 2017\nNews for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).\n\n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n\n-LAS VEGAS SHOOTING UPDATE\n-LAS VEGAS SHOOTER HAD GUNS AND EXPLOSIVES \n-TRUMP VISITS PUERTO RICO\n-PUERTO RICO STILL STRUGGLING\n-FORMER EQUIFAX CEO TESTIFIES ON CAPITOL HILL\n-ROCK LEGEND TOM PETTY DIES\n-COP SAVES SKUNK FROM MCFLURRY CUP\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such a",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 13.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 13.0, \"end\": 19.0, \"text\": \"I am Candace Jones. And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 23.0, \"end\": 28.0, \"text\": \"On Sunday in Las Vegas at\"}, {\"start\": 28.0, \"end\": 32.0, \"text\": \"the Mandalay Bay Hotel a man on the 32nd\"}, {\"start\": 32.0, \"end\": 37.0, \"text\": \"floor peered down at a crowd of people who were enjoying a\"}, {\"start\": 37.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"concert. The man\"}, {\"start\": 43.0, \"end\": 47.0, \"text\": \"opened fire on throngs of people below. A\"}, {\"start\": 47.0, \"end\": 52.0, \"text\": \"total of 59 people died. Here are pictures of some of the victims.\"}, {\"start\": 54.0, \"end\": 59.0, \"text\": \"Five hundred twenty seven people were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 59.0, \"end\": 63.0, \"text\": \"Police have identified the shooter as Stephen Paddock.\"}, {\"start\": 67.0, \"end\": 72.0, \"text\": \"Police still don't know why he did it.\"}, {\"start\": 72.0, \"end\": 77.0, \"text\": \"When police confronted Paddock to arrest him\"}, {\"start\": 77.0, \"end\": 82.0, \"text\": \"he killed himself before police could\"}, {\"start\": 82.0, \"end\": 83.0, \"text\": \"question him.\"}, {\"start\": 88.0, \"end\": 93.0, \"text\": \"Police searched Paddock's home and his hotel room.\"}, {\"start\": 93.0, \"end\": 98.0, \"text\": \"What they found was shocking.\"}, {\"start\": 98.0, \"end\": 103.0, \"text\": \"At his home police found at least 19 firearms\"}, {\"start\": 108.0, \"end\": 112.0, \"text\": \"and several thousand rounds of bullets.\"}, {\"start\": 114.0, \"end\": 118.0, \"text\": \"In his hotel room police found 23 weapons\"}, {\"start\": 118.0, \"end\": 122.0, \"text\": \"including a handgun, multiple rifles and\"}, {\"start\": 125.0, \"end\": 129.0, \"text\": \"several pounds of ammonium nitrate.\"}, {\"start\": 130.0, \"end\": 133.0, \"text\": \"It is used to make bombs. It was found in Paddock's car.\"}, {\"start\": 137.0, \"end\": 142.0, \"text\": \"Today President Trump and his wife First\"}, {\"start\": 142.0, \"end\": 147.0, \"text\": \"Lady Melania Trump arrived in Puerto Rico.\"}, {\"start\": 148.0, \"end\": 151.0, \"text\": \"Hurricane Maria destroyed the island.\"}, {\"start\": 153.0, \"end\": 159.0, \"text\": \"The two of them got to see the destruction firsthand.\"}, {\"start\": 159.0, \"end\": 163.0, \"text\": \"President Trump met with Puerto Rican government officials to\"}, {\"start\": 163.0, \"end\": 169.0, \"text\": \"discuss ways to help the island get back on its feet.\"}, {\"start\": 169.0, \"end\": 174.0, \"text\": \"And President Trump met with some of the people\"}, {\"start\": 174.0, \"end\": 179.0, \"text\": \"affected by the storm. The people of Puerto Rico are\"}, {\"start\": 179.0, \"end\": 184.0, \"text\": \"hoping the president's visit will speed up the\"}, {\"start\": 184.0, \"end\": 188.0, \"text\": \"federal funding needed to recover from the storm.\"}, {\"start\": 194.0, \"end\": 198.0, \"text\": \"It's been nearly two weeks since Hurricane Maria\"}, {\"start\": 198.0, \"end\": 203.0, \"text\": \"slammed Puerto Rico. The conditions there --\"}, {\"start\": 203.0, \"end\": 208.0, \"text\": \"homes, businesses, schools, hospitals -- are\"}, {\"start\": 208.0, \"end\": 214.0, \"text\": \"slowly starting to improve.\"}, {\"start\": 215.0, \"end\": 220.0, \"text\": \"The number of people with electricity is slowly ticking upward.\"}, {\"start\": 220.0, \"end\": 224.0, \"text\": \"But connecting to cell service or the internet\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 230.0, \"text\": \"is still difficult. At some gas\"}, {\"start\": 230.0, \"end\": 234.0, \"text\": \"stations and grocery stores long lines\"}, {\"start\": 234.0, \"end\": 237.0, \"text\": \"continue to snake around the city.\"}, {\"start\": 240.0, \"end\": 244.0, \"text\": \"And a lot of the drinking water is still dirty\"}, {\"start\": 245.0, \"end\": 250.0, \"text\": \"and contaminated. People cannot drink most of it. Only 45\"}, {\"start\": 250.0, \"end\": 254.0, \"text\": \"percent of the residents have clean water. Here is Puerto Rico's governor\"}, {\"start\": 254.0, \"end\": 259.0, \"text\": \"Ricardo Rosello, with the help of an interpreter,\"}, {\"start\": 259.0, \"end\": 264.0, \"text\": \"explaining that there is still a lot of work to do.\"}, {\"start\": 271.0, \"end\": 276.0, \"text\": \"I would like to reiterate our priorities are still to sustain and\"}, {\"start\": 276.0, \"end\": 281.0, \"text\": \"maintain lives. Making sure water and food get to different areas of\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 286.0, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico, the distribution of fuel, maintenance and operations of\"}, {\"start\": 286.0, \"end\": 290.0, \"text\": \"hospitals, elevating and restoring telecom\"}, {\"start\": 291.0, \"end\": 296.0, \"text\": \"in Puerto Rico, elevating and restoring water and sewer and\"}, {\"start\": 296.0, \"end\": 298.0, \"text\": \"start the restoration process.\"}, {\"start\": 301.0, \"end\": 306.0, \"text\": \"Today in Washington D.C. former Equifax\"}, {\"start\": 308.0, \"end\": 312.0, \"text\": \"CEO Richard Smith\"}, {\"start\": 314.0, \"end\": 318.0, \"text\": \"testified about the company's massive\"}, {\"start\": 318.0, \"end\": 323.0, \"text\": \"information breach. Smith told the House\"}, {\"start\": 323.0, \"end\": 327.0, \"text\": \"Commerce Committee that he apologized for the\"}, {\"start\": 327.0, \"end\": 332.0, \"text\": \"breach. He said human error and technology failures\"}, {\"start\": 332.0, \"end\": 337.0, \"text\": \"are to blame for what happened. Equifax says about\"}, {\"start\": 337.0, \"end\": 342.0, \"text\": \"145-million people may have been impacted\"}, {\"start\": 342.0, \"end\": 343.0, \"text\": \"by the breach.\"}, {\"start\": 342.0, \"end\": 347.0, \"text\": \"Their sensitive personal information like Social Security numbers,\"}, {\"start\": 347.0, \"end\": 355.0, \"text\": \"addreses and driver's license information could be exposed by the breach.\"}, {\"start\": 357.0, \"end\": 361.0, \"text\": \"On Monday rock legend Tom Petty\"}, {\"start\": 362.0, \"end\": 367.0, \"text\": \"died. On Sunday night\"}, {\"start\": 368.0, \"end\": 373.0, \"text\": \"Petty was found unconscious in his home and was rushed to the\"}, {\"start\": 373.0, \"end\": 378.0, \"text\": \"hospital. He was 66 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 379.0, \"end\": 384.0, \"text\": \"In 1975. Petit formed the group\"}, {\"start\": 384.0, \"end\": 393.0, \"text\": \"Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers.\"}, {\"start\": 395.0, \"end\": 397.0, \"text\": \"Many music fans\"}, {\"start\": 397.0, \"end\": 400.0, \"text\": \"say Tom Petty and The Heartbreakers\"}, {\"start\": 400.0, \"end\": 407.0, \"text\": \"was the best rock n roll band in the world.\"}, {\"start\": 408.0, \"end\": 414.0, \"text\": \"For years the group performed together\"}, {\"start\": 415.0, \"end\": 419.0, \"text\": \"but later Petty became a solo act.\"}, {\"start\": 419.0, \"end\": 424.0, \"text\": \"Petty's music legacy\"}, {\"start\": 426.0, \"end\": 434.0, \"text\": \"includes numerous albums --\"}, {\"start\": 435.0, \"end\": 439.0, \"text\": \"more than of 25.\"}, {\"start\": 440.0, \"end\": 444.0, \"text\": \"Petty also won countless awards\"}, {\"start\": 445.0, \"end\": 450.0, \"text\": \"including 3 Grammy awards.\"}, {\"start\": 451.0, \"end\": 455.0, \"text\": \"In 2002 Tom Petty\"}, {\"start\": 455.0, \"end\": 459.0, \"text\": \"and The Heartbreakers were\"}, {\"start\": 459.0, \"end\": 463.0, \"text\": \"inducted into the Rock n Roll\"}, {\"start\": 464.0, \"end\": 470.0, \"text\": \"Hall of Fame.\"}, {\"start\": 472.0, \"end\": 476.0, \"text\": \"In Maine a police officer by the name of\"}, {\"start\": 476.0, \"end\": 485.0, \"text\": \"David McKinnon became friends with a skunk.\"}, {\"start\": 486.0, \"end\": 490.0, \"text\": \"The skunk's got its head stuck\"}, {\"start\": 490.0, \"end\": 498.0, \"text\": \"in a McDonald's MC flurry Cup.\"}, {\"start\": 499.0, \"end\": 503.0, \"text\": \"The officer knew if he tried to help he might\"}, {\"start\": 504.0, \"end\": 507.0, \"text\": \"be sprayed with skunk funk.\"}, {\"start\": 507.0, \"end\": 513.0, \"text\": \"But he did it anyway.\"}, {\"start\": 514.0, \"end\": 517.0, \"text\": \"Once the skunk was free it looked like it was getting ready to spray\"}, {\"start\": 518.0, \"end\": 522.0, \"text\": \"but changed its mind and scampered off.\"}, {\"start\": 523.0, \"end\": 527.0, \"text\": \"The video was posted on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 527.0, \"end\": 531.0, \"text\": \"People saw the good deeds of the police officer\"}, {\"start\": 531.0, \"end\": 534.0, \"text\": \"and the video spread like wildfire.\"}, {\"start\": 534.0, \"end\": 536.0, \"text\": \"Thousands of people have viewed it.\"}, {\"start\": 539.0, \"end\": 544.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 544.0, \"end\": 551.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "so9BbSfdQGM": {
    "video_id": "so9BbSfdQGM",
    "title": "50th anniversary of MLK, Jr. assassination (ASL - 4.4.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180405",
    "duration": 60,
    "view_count": 392,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.8, \"end\": 13.02, \"text\": \"Today marks the 50th anniversary of the assassination of civil rights leader Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr.\"}, {\"start\": 13.02, \"end\": 23.8, \"text\": \"He was shot to death on the balcony of the Lorraine Motel in Memphis, Tennessee in 1968.\"}, {\"start\": 23.88, \"end\": 34.08, \"text\": \"Cities across the country honored him with ceremonies, performances and peaceful marches.\"}, {\"start\": 34.08, \"end\": 42.68, \"text\": \"Several cities also rang bells 39 times, symbolizing King's age at the time of his death.\"}, {\"start\": 42.68, \"end\": 48.44, \"text\": \"The bells rang around the time King was shot, 7pm.\"}, {\"start\": 48.46, \"end\": 54.92, \"text\": \"Various speakers challenged listeners to push for justice and equality just as King would\"}, {\"start\": 54.92, \"end\": 58.3, \"text\": \"have if he were still alive today.\"}]"
  },
  "Ai0_0EEvMXo": {
    "video_id": "Ai0_0EEvMXo",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.2.2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171203",
    "duration": 418,
    "view_count": 228,
    "description": "December 2, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n -SENATE PASSES GOP TAX BILL\n-TRUMP NOT WORRIED ABOUT FLYNN GUILTY PLEA\n-MAN ARMED WITH RIFLE WARNED OF 'LIZARD PEOPLE'\n-SMARTPHONE ADDICTIONS COULD CHANGE YOUR BRAIN\n-NETFLIX \"STRANGER THINGS\" IS COMING BACK\n-CHRIS PRATT AND ANNA FARIS FILE FOR DIVORCE\n-NISSAN UNVEILS 'STAR WARS' THEMED VEHICLES\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality n",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.38, \"end\": 8.68, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.7, \"end\": 10.0, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 10.0, \"end\": 12.34, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 13.48, \"end\": 24.1, \"text\": \"After hours of debate, last-minute changes and one Republican holdout,\"}, {\"start\": 24.12, \"end\": 26.66, \"text\": \"the Senate passed its version of a tax reform today.\"}, {\"start\": 26.78, \"end\": 32.66, \"text\": \"The bill passed by 51 to 49 vote.\"}, {\"start\": 32.7, \"end\": 40.58, \"text\": \"An analysis suggests if the bill becomes law, more than $1 trillion could be added to the\"}, {\"start\": 40.62, \"end\": 49.74, \"text\": \"deficit over 10 years.\"}, {\"start\": 49.76, \"end\": 55.26, \"text\": \"Now the bill will head to the House.\"}, {\"start\": 55.26, \"end\": 58.72, \"text\": \"The House passed its own tax reform bill last month.\"}, {\"start\": 61.56, \"end\": 66.7, \"text\": \"Republicans hope to combine the two so a final version can be sent to President Trump for\"}, {\"start\": 66.76, \"end\": 69.96, \"text\": \"his signature before Christmas.\"}, {\"start\": 71.54, \"end\": 78.74, \"text\": \"Today President Trump said he is not worried about what his former National Security Advisor\"}, {\"start\": 78.74, \"end\": 90.32, \"text\": \"Michael Flynn might tell Special Counsel Robert Mueller.\"}, {\"start\": 90.32, \"end\": 98.16, \"text\": \"Mueller's team is investigating Russia's efforts to influence last year's election.\"}, {\"start\": 98.24, \"end\": 102.78, \"text\": \"The President says he has no concerns about the inquiry.\"}, {\"start\": 102.78, \"end\": 106.6, \"text\": \"Trump says there has been absolutely no collusion.\"}, {\"start\": 106.62, \"end\": 112.1, \"text\": \"Flynn pleaded guilty yesterday to lying to the FBI\"}, {\"start\": 112.14, \"end\": 115.98, \"text\": \"about conversations with Russia's ambassador.\"}, {\"start\": 116.06, \"end\": 118.8, \"text\": \"The former National Security Advisor for the Trump administration is cooperating with the\"}, {\"start\": 118.84, \"end\": 121.28, \"text\": \"special counsel's office.\"}, {\"start\": 123.8, \"end\": 130.2, \"text\": \"Police in Washington state responded to a bizarre scene.\"}, {\"start\": 130.3, \"end\": 135.24, \"text\": \"Last Saturday, they received a report of a man parking his SUV in the middle of an intersection\"}, {\"start\": 135.24, \"end\": 138.9, \"text\": \"and waving around a rifle and handgun.\"}, {\"start\": 138.9, \"end\": 143.82, \"text\": \"He rambled to responding police about \\\"lizard people.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 143.88, \"end\": 149.02, \"text\": \"Police had to tase them twice to get them to comply.\"}, {\"start\": 149.02, \"end\": 154.58, \"text\": \"Police detained him and found a stash of weapons in his car:\"}, {\"start\": 154.64, \"end\": 169.48, \"text\": \"including a loaded AK-47 rifle, a loaded 357 revolver, five loaded magazines,\"}, {\"start\": 169.48, \"end\": 175.98, \"text\": \"a wooden bat and 170 rounds of ammo.\"}, {\"start\": 176.06, \"end\": 186.22, \"text\": \"Police say he told them he took meth to lose weight and was taking prescription morphine.\"}, {\"start\": 186.28, \"end\": 192.44, \"text\": \"He also said President Trump called him at his home and warned him about lizard people.\"}, {\"start\": 192.5, \"end\": 198.62, \"text\": \"Authorities say the 54-year-old man was heavily influenced by a stimulant.\"}, {\"start\": 198.68, \"end\": 203.84, \"text\": \"He was taken to the hospital for a 14-day mental health evaluation.\"}, {\"start\": 205.54, \"end\": 214.96, \"text\": \"A new study says cell phone addiction is real and it could affect the way your brain works.\"}, {\"start\": 214.98, \"end\": 222.9, \"text\": \"Researchers in South Korea studied brain images from 19 teenage boys\"}, {\"start\": 222.9, \"end\": 227.76, \"text\": \"who had been diagnosed with internet or smart phone addiction,\"}, {\"start\": 227.78, \"end\": 233.04, \"text\": \"then compare them with brain images from 19 teens who were not addicted.\"}, {\"start\": 233.1, \"end\": 242.78, \"text\": \"Researchers found that the brains of addicted boys had higher levels of a neurotransmitter\"}, {\"start\": 242.78, \"end\": 244.3, \"text\": \"called GABA.\"}, {\"start\": 244.34, \"end\": 256.32, \"text\": \"GABA slows down neurons in the brain and can make it hard to focus.\"}, {\"start\": 256.38, \"end\": 262.46, \"text\": \"The findings align with other studies that indicate smart phone and internet addiction\"}, {\"start\": 262.54, \"end\": 266.98, \"text\": \"can harm the mind.\"}, {\"start\": 268.32, \"end\": 275.18, \"text\": \"The hit series \\\"Stranger Things\\\" is coming back.\"}, {\"start\": 275.26, \"end\": 283.34, \"text\": \"Netflix announced Friday that its popular series have been renewed for a third season.\"}, {\"start\": 283.44, \"end\": 285.6, \"text\": \"It's been a good year for \\\"Stranger Things.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 285.64, \"end\": 291.22, \"text\": \"Its second season debuted in October to rave reviews.\"}, {\"start\": 291.3, \"end\": 298.64, \"text\": \"The show picked up five Emmys and a SAG award earlier this year.\"}, {\"start\": 298.68, \"end\": 304.5, \"text\": \"No release date for the third season has been set yet.\"}, {\"start\": 306.2, \"end\": 314.92, \"text\": \"Actor Chris Pratt, best known for his \\\"Guardians of the Galaxy\\\" role,\"}, {\"start\": 314.92, \"end\": 318.76, \"text\": \"has filed divorce from his wife Anna Faris,\"}, {\"start\": 318.8, \"end\": 328.08, \"text\": \"best known for her role in the \\\"Scary Movie\\\" sequels -- citing irreconcilable differences.\"}, {\"start\": 328.12, \"end\": 330.32, \"text\": \"The couple had been married for eight years.\"}, {\"start\": 330.32, \"end\": 339.96, \"text\": \"Pratt is seeking joint custody of their five-year-old son Jack.\"}, {\"start\": 341.62, \"end\": 350.36, \"text\": \"Nissan went all out with its \\\"Star Wars\\\" tie-in at the Los Angeles auto show.\"}, {\"start\": 350.44, \"end\": 356.92, \"text\": \"Last year Nissan produced one \\\"Star Wars\\\" themed vehicle for the event to tie-in to\"}, {\"start\": 356.98, \"end\": 360.54, \"text\": \"the release of the movie \\\"Rogue One.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 360.58, \"end\": 370.42, \"text\": \"This year Nissan made 7 themed cars to promote the upcoming film \\\"The Last Jedi.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 370.44, \"end\": 374.74, \"text\": \"One car is made to look like an AT-M6.\"}, {\"start\": 374.94, \"end\": 378.48, \"text\": \"Another car made to look like a Kylo Ren theme.\"}, {\"start\": 378.5, \"end\": 383.14, \"text\": \"And another one has additions to make it look like a \\\"Tie-Fighter.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 383.22, \"end\": 386.72, \"text\": \"The vehicles are not for sale though.\"}, {\"start\": 386.76, \"end\": 395.28, \"text\": \"They were created to promote the brand and show how Nissan cars can be customized.\"}, {\"start\": 397.56, \"end\": 399.36, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 399.38, \"end\": 402.62, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 402.7, \"end\": 406.92, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 406.98, \"end\": 412.64, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "k7RAvMHIHf0": {
    "video_id": "k7RAvMHIHf0",
    "title": "Sheriff heard on recording saying “take him out!” (ASL - 2.11.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180212",
    "duration": 115,
    "view_count": 166,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.38, \"end\": 11.88, \"text\": \"Last April, officers attempted to pull over a 33-year-old white male named Michael Dial.\"}, {\"start\": 11.98, \"end\": 17.54, \"text\": \"This is video of the chase.\"}, {\"start\": 17.54, \"end\": 21.1, \"text\": \"They suspected him of driving with a suspended license.\"}, {\"start\": 21.1, \"end\": 23.92, \"text\": \"But he kept on driving.\"}, {\"start\": 23.92, \"end\": 25.32, \"text\": \"This was not a high-speed chase.\"}, {\"start\": 25.32, \"end\": 27.94, \"text\": \"Officers say they never went faster than 50 miles per hour.\"}, {\"start\": 27.94, \"end\": 33.76, \"text\": \"Eventually they used a pit maneuver to force Dial's truck off the road.\"}, {\"start\": 33.76, \"end\": 40.64, \"text\": \"Witnesses say Dial never posed a threat to the public, but orders came from White County\"}, {\"start\": 40.64, \"end\": 51.68, \"text\": \"Sheriff Oddie Shoupe over the radio to \\\"take him out\\\" by any means necessary, including\"}, {\"start\": 51.68, \"end\": 54.34, \"text\": \"deadly force.\"}, {\"start\": 54.34, \"end\": 57.88, \"text\": \"About a minute later shots were fired and Dial was killed.\"}, {\"start\": 57.88, \"end\": 63.32, \"text\": \"Shoupe was not involved in the chase and he didn't see any danger Dial may or may not\"}, {\"start\": 63.32, \"end\": 64.62, \"text\": \"have presented.\"}, {\"start\": 64.62, \"end\": 73.32, \"text\": \"But when Shoupe arrived on the scene later, one of the officer's body cams was left on\"}, {\"start\": 73.32, \"end\": 75.68, \"text\": \"and, unbeknownst to Shoupe, he was recorded saying this:\"}, {\"start\": 92.9, \"end\": 100.02, \"text\": \"Shoupe seems to suggest he would rather his officers shoot and kill Dial rather than damage\"}, {\"start\": 100.02, \"end\": 102.02, \"text\": \"their patrol cars.\"}, {\"start\": 102.02, \"end\": 107.44, \"text\": \"The district attorney ruled the shooting justified.\"}, {\"start\": 107.44, \"end\": 114.54, \"text\": \"But Dial's widow has filed a federal lawsuit against the parties involved.\"}]"
  },
  "XLmvwuD9QEo": {
    "video_id": "XLmvwuD9QEo",
    "title": "Dr. G answers your questions: How do Deaf people avoid touching our faces?",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200408",
    "duration": 80,
    "view_count": 582,
    "description": "Posted 4.8.20",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.62, \"end\": 1.94, \"text\": \"Hello again!\"}, {\"start\": 1.94, \"end\": 5.76, \"text\": \"I am Dr. G, a hearing family physician.\"}, {\"start\": 5.76, \"end\": 11.5, \"text\": \"I have many Deaf patients and I am getting many, many questions.\"}, {\"start\": 11.54, \"end\": 15.28, \"text\": \"Today is want to answer some of your questions.\"}, {\"start\": 15.28, \"end\": 19.0, \"text\": \"The first question comes from Lee Handler.\"}, {\"start\": 19.0, \"end\": 27.0, \"text\": \"He wants to know how can Deaf people avoid touching their faces when they sign.\"}, {\"start\": 27.0, \"end\": 29.0, \"text\": \"It's impossible.\"}, {\"start\": 29.0, \"end\": 32.48, \"text\": \"Really I had two responses to that question.\"}, {\"start\": 32.5, \"end\": 38.84, \"text\": \"The first is when you're at home it's okay to touch your face but wash your hands thoroughly\"}, {\"start\": 38.84, \"end\": 42.0, \"text\": \"for about 20 minutes (sic seconds) before touching your face.\"}, {\"start\": 42.0, \"end\": 49.52, \"text\": \"But if you go out and you're not sure if you washed your hands, stop.\"}, {\"start\": 49.6, \"end\": 52.0, \"text\": \"Do not touch your face.\"}, {\"start\": 52.0, \"end\": 59.06, \"text\": \"Actually you can sign without touching by stopping just a little before you get to your face.\"}, {\"start\": 59.06, \"end\": 63.5, \"text\": \"For example you can sign the word \\\"say\\\" near your chin but don't touch your chin.\"}, {\"start\": 63.6, \"end\": 69.0, \"text\": \"I know it's hard but that will help you.\"}, {\"start\": 69.0, \"end\": 74.0, \"text\": \"If you broke your arm you can still sign using one hand right?\"}, {\"start\": 74.0, \"end\": 79.0, \"text\": \"I know it's hard and probably not clear but you can make it work.\"}]"
  },
  "UMTmgiJcGXs": {
    "video_id": "UMTmgiJcGXs",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.18.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171119",
    "duration": 407,
    "view_count": 242,
    "description": "November 18, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-MUELLER WILL INTERVIEW TOP MEMBER OF TRUMP'S INNER CIRCLE\n-GOP TAX PLAN: WHAT'S NEXT?\n-PITTSBURGH COP KILLED, REWARD OFFERED FOR INFO \n-THREE INMATES ESCAPE THROUGH LIBRARY CEILING\n-RYAN SEACREST COMMENTS ON MISCONDUCT ALLEGATIONS\n-NASA LAUNCHES WEATHER SATELLITE\n-HAPPY 89TH BIRTHDAY MICKEY MOUSE\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 11.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.0, \"end\": 22.0, \"text\": \"Special Counsel Robert Mueller continues his investigation\"}, {\"start\": 23.0, \"end\": 26.0, \"text\": \"into Russia's meddling into the 2016 presidential election.\"}, {\"start\": 27.0, \"end\": 33.0, \"text\": \"Now he's turned his attention to a woman\"}, {\"start\": 33.124, \"end\": 36.024, \"text\": \"named Hope Hicks.\"}, {\"start\": 36.1, \"end\": 44.0, \"text\": \"She was a key point person when Trump launched his\"}, {\"start\": 44.0, \"end\": 49.0, \"text\": \"campaign in 2015 and she's been in the room for some\"}, {\"start\": 49.0, \"end\": 55.0, \"text\": \"of the most controversial decisions. She is never far from the president's side.\"}, {\"start\": 55.024, \"end\": 56.999, \"text\": \"The 29 year old is now the\"}, {\"start\": 57.0, \"end\": 62.0, \"text\": \"White House communications director working\"}, {\"start\": 62.0, \"end\": 65.0, \"text\": \"from a desk right outside the Oval Office.\"}, {\"start\": 65.0, \"end\": 70.0, \"text\": \"Her prime place on the president's team\"}, {\"start\": 71.0, \"end\": 75.0, \"text\": \"has made her of interest to Mueller.\"}, {\"start\": 75.0, \"end\": 80.0, \"text\": \"Mueller's team plans to interview Hicks before the end of the month.\"}, {\"start\": 83.0, \"end\": 88.0, \"text\": \"As soon as the Thanksgiving break is over\"}, {\"start\": 88.0, \"end\": 92.0, \"text\": \"the new Republican tax plan will be the first thing on the Senate's agenda.\"}, {\"start\": 92.0, \"end\": 97.0, \"text\": \"Despite a rapid move by the House to pass the tax bill\"}, {\"start\": 98.0, \"end\": 103.0, \"text\": \"the fight in the Senate may pack more punches.\"}, {\"start\": 103.0, \"end\": 107.0, \"text\": \"Senate Republicans have only a thin majority already.\"}, {\"start\": 108.0, \"end\": 114.0, \"text\": \"Republican Senator Ron Johnson of Wisconsin\"}, {\"start\": 114.0, \"end\": 118.0, \"text\": \"says he's opposed to the bill and there are\"}, {\"start\": 118.0, \"end\": 123.0, \"text\": \"several Republicans who are on the fence. They are\"}, {\"start\": 124.0, \"end\": 129.0, \"text\": \"concerned about adding to the federal deficit. If senators do pass\"}, {\"start\": 129.0, \"end\": 134.0, \"text\": \"the bill it still has to battle back in the House.\"}, {\"start\": 135.0, \"end\": 139.0, \"text\": \"But the White House says  it is sure the tax plan will\"}, {\"start\": 139.0, \"end\": 141.0, \"text\": \"soon be the law of the land.\"}, {\"start\": 145.0, \"end\": 150.0, \"text\": \"Last night Pittsburgh police officer Brian Shaw was killed\"}, {\"start\": 150.0, \"end\": 154.0, \"text\": \"in the line of duty after pulling over a car. Investigators say the person\"}, {\"start\": 155.0, \"end\": 159.0, \"text\": \"in the car jumped out and ran. Shaw followed.\"}, {\"start\": 159.0, \"end\": 165.0, \"text\": \"The suspect fired at Shaw. He was struck in the chest and killed.\"}, {\"start\": 165.0, \"end\": 170.0, \"text\": \"The shooter got away. Shaw had been on the force for less than a year.\"}, {\"start\": 170.0, \"end\": 175.0, \"text\": \"Now police are asking for the public's help to find his killer.\"}, {\"start\": 175.0, \"end\": 183.0, \"text\": \"They are offering a $40,000 reward to anyone with information.\"}, {\"start\": 183.0, \"end\": 187.0, \"text\": \"Of the $40,000 reward, $25,000 came from the FBI,\"}, {\"start\": 188.0, \"end\": 193.0, \"text\": \"$10,000 came from the ATF and $5,000 from the\"}, {\"start\": 193.0, \"end\": 198.0, \"text\": \"U.S. Marshalls Service.\"}, {\"start\": 200.0, \"end\": 205.0, \"text\": \"A manhunt is underway for three Florida\"}, {\"start\": 205.0, \"end\": 211.0, \"text\": \"inmates. Joel Cooper,\"}, {\"start\": 211.0, \"end\": 215.0, \"text\": \"Donald Cotterman and\"}, {\"start\": 215.0, \"end\": 219.0, \"text\": \"Casey Martina escaped from the\"}, {\"start\": 220.0, \"end\": 224.0, \"text\": \"Wakulla county jail. Deputies say the inmates\"}, {\"start\": 225.0, \"end\": 230.0, \"text\": \"got out through the ceiling in the jail's library.\"}, {\"start\": 230.0, \"end\": 236.0, \"text\": \"They were serving sentences for burglary and other crimes.\"}, {\"start\": 236.0, \"end\": 241.0, \"text\": \"Deputies say they have received a number of tips and investigators are following up\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 246.0, \"text\": \"on them. But there are  indications the inmates are no longer in the county.\"}, {\"start\": 252.0, \"end\": 256.0, \"text\": \"The E cable channel has launched an investigation into alleged\"}, {\"start\": 256.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"misconduct by Ryan Seacrest. The alleged incident occurred about a\"}, {\"start\": 261.0, \"end\": 265.0, \"text\": \"decade ago when Seacrest worked at the channel.\"}, {\"start\": 266.0, \"end\": 271.0, \"text\": \"The accuser is a former stylist who worked at E with Seacrest while he was there.\"}, {\"start\": 271.0, \"end\": 275.0, \"text\": \"In a statement Seacrest said if he made the stylist\"}, {\"start\": 275.0, \"end\": 278.0, \"text\": \"feel anything but respected he is truly sorry.\"}, {\"start\": 278.024, \"end\": 280.924, \"text\": \"However Seacrest says he disputes the allegations\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 284.0, \"text\": \"and will cooperate in any investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 284.024, \"end\": 288.024, \"text\": \"He also called himself an advocate for women.\"}, {\"start\": 291.0, \"end\": 296.0, \"text\": \"Forecasters are hoping that this satellite\"}, {\"start\": 296.024, \"end\": 300.024, \"text\": \"will help them track future hurricanes.\"}, {\"start\": 300.1, \"end\": 303.1, \"text\": \"The Joint Polar Satellite System One\"}, {\"start\": 304.0, \"end\": 310.0, \"text\": \"was launched from Vandenberg Air Force\"}, {\"start\": 310.0, \"end\": 314.0, \"text\": \"California Saturday morning. It's the first in a series of four\"}, {\"start\": 314.0, \"end\": 317.0, \"text\": \"U.S. weather satellites. It's expected to help  meteorologists\"}, {\"start\": 317.024, \"end\": 319.024, \"text\": \"not only make more accurate weather forecasts\"}, {\"start\": 320.0, \"end\": 324.0, \"text\": \"but also help them better predict where future hurricanes are headed.\"}, {\"start\": 324.024, \"end\": 326.024, \"text\": \"Emergency workers will use the images from space\"}, {\"start\": 329.0, \"end\": 334.0, \"text\": \"as well to visualize the damage and power outages after storms.\"}, {\"start\": 337.0, \"end\": 342.0, \"text\": \"Mickey Mouse turned\"}, {\"start\": 342.0, \"end\": 345.0, \"text\": \"89 years today. His first cartoon\"}, {\"start\": 345.0, \"end\": 349.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Steamboat Willie\\\" premiered\"}, {\"start\": 351.0, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"in New York on November 18, 1928.\"}, {\"start\": 354.0, \"end\": 358.0, \"text\": \"Mickey's official birthday has actually changed a number of times over the years.\"}, {\"start\": 358.0, \"end\": 363.0, \"text\": \"But according to the Walt Disney Family Museum it was\"}, {\"start\": 363.0, \"end\": 370.0, \"text\": \"settled in 1978 that the star was born on his first big movie premiere.\"}, {\"start\": 371.0, \"end\": 375.0, \"text\": \"Of course that makes November 18th Minnie Mouse's birthday\"}, {\"start\": 375.0, \"end\": 379.0, \"text\": \"as well because she appeared in the same cartoon.\"}, {\"start\": 379.024, \"end\": 381.024, \"text\": \"So happy birthday to both.\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 387.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 387.0, \"end\": 389.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 389.001, \"end\": 393.001, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 393.1, \"end\": 398.1, \"text\": \"Sign1 News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "1shDjV2kuYI": {
    "video_id": "1shDjV2kuYI",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.3.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180404",
    "duration": 748,
    "view_count": 996,
    "description": "4.3.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Man suspected in killing of wealthy grandfather\n-18 states sue Trump Administration over census\n-First jail sentence in Russia investigation\n-Trump shifts back to hard-line immigration stance\n-Legalizing pot could help opioid crisis \n-Dining out may disrupt your hormones\n-Weird weather in April\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.92, \"end\": 9.62, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.62, \"end\": 11.8, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.8, \"end\": 13.22, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.22, \"end\": 16.96, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.46, \"end\": 27.62, \"text\": \"Nathan Carman appeared in a New Hampshire Court today.\"}, {\"start\": 27.76, \"end\": 40.26, \"text\": \"He is suspected in the death of John Chakalos, Carman's wealthy grandfather.\"}, {\"start\": 40.26, \"end\": 55.48, \"text\": \"Carman, who is representing himself in court, pleaded the fifth when asked about weapons\"}, {\"start\": 55.48, \"end\": 58.12, \"text\": \"he might own.\"}, {\"start\": 58.12, \"end\": 69.02, \"text\": \"Attorneys were inquiring about a rifle that has been missing since the grandfather was\"}, {\"start\": 69.02, \"end\": 71.08, \"text\": \"shot to death in 2013.\"}, {\"start\": 71.08, \"end\": 84.38, \"text\": \"The missing weapon has the same caliber of ammunition as the weapon that was used to\"}, {\"start\": 84.38, \"end\": 86.28, \"text\": \"kill Chakalos.\"}, {\"start\": 86.28, \"end\": 95.76, \"text\": \"While police have named Carman as a suspect, he hasn't been charged.\"}, {\"start\": 95.76, \"end\": 108.94, \"text\": \"But Carman's aunts are taking legal action to deny him access to his inheritance because\"}, {\"start\": 108.94, \"end\": 120.58, \"text\": \"they say he was also responsible for the death of his mother, who has been missing ever since\"}, {\"start\": 120.64, \"end\": 123.28, \"text\": \"the boat she and Carman were on sank in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 123.28, \"end\": 133.36, \"text\": \"Carman spent eight days on a life raft before being rescued.\"}, {\"start\": 133.36, \"end\": 138.3, \"text\": \"His mother's body was never found.\"}, {\"start\": 141.86, \"end\": 156.9, \"text\": \"The Trump administration wants to demand citizenship information on the next census in 2020.\"}, {\"start\": 156.9, \"end\": 162.38, \"text\": \"But if 18 states have their way, that won't happen.\"}, {\"start\": 162.42, \"end\": 171.7, \"text\": \"A multi-state federal lawsuit has been filed to block the Trump administration from asking\"}, {\"start\": 171.7, \"end\": 174.24, \"text\": \"a question about citizenship.\"}, {\"start\": 174.24, \"end\": 186.12, \"text\": \"Those states say adding a citizenship question will greatly reduce the level of participation\"}, {\"start\": 186.12, \"end\": 200.7, \"text\": \"in the census and would end up costing states tens of millions of dollars in federal funding\"}, {\"start\": 200.7, \"end\": 206.64, \"text\": \"for education and infrastructure.\"}, {\"start\": 206.64, \"end\": 227.42, \"text\": \"The Trump administration says the citizenship question will help enforce voting rights.\"}, {\"start\": 230.94, \"end\": 245.84, \"text\": \"Dutch lawyer Alex Van der Zwaan is the first person in the Russia investigation to go to jail.\"}, {\"start\": 245.98, \"end\": 255.72, \"text\": \"Today a federal judge decided he will spend 30 days in jail and must also pay a $20,000 fine.\"}, {\"start\": 255.8, \"end\": 275.2, \"text\": \"Van der Zwaan is tied to former Trump deputy campaign chairman Rick Gates.\"}, {\"start\": 275.2, \"end\": 287.62, \"text\": \"Gates admitted to lying to special counsel Robert Mueller's team.\"}, {\"start\": 287.62, \"end\": 301.38, \"text\": \"Van der Zwaan pleaded guilty to lying to Mueller's team in February.\"}, {\"start\": 301.38, \"end\": 311.54, \"text\": \"During Tuesday's sentencing, a prosecutor told the judge Van der Zwaan should be made\"}, {\"start\": 311.54, \"end\": 313.6, \"text\": \"an example of.\"}, {\"start\": 319.1, \"end\": 331.02, \"text\": \"In the last 48 hours President Trump has tweeted 10 times about illegal immigration.\"}, {\"start\": 331.12, \"end\": 336.92, \"text\": \"He continues to complain about US immigration policies, calling current laws \\\"weak\\\" and\"}, {\"start\": 336.92, \"end\": 346.4, \"text\": \"an \\\"Obama joke\\\" and urging Congress to act.\"}, {\"start\": 346.4, \"end\": 358.2, \"text\": \"This after sources say a number of the president's allies warned him this weekend that his support\"}, {\"start\": 358.2, \"end\": 361.38, \"text\": \"base thinks he's softening on immigration.\"}, {\"start\": 361.38, \"end\": 369.76, \"text\": \"So the White House is beginning another push to pass a series of hardline measures that\"}, {\"start\": 369.76, \"end\": 384.04, \"text\": \"failed to gain steam last fall.\"}, {\"start\": 384.06, \"end\": 396.54, \"text\": \"Those measures include removing protections that prevent the immediate deportation of\"}, {\"start\": 396.54, \"end\": 403.22, \"text\": \"undocumented children and allowing authorities to keep families\"}, {\"start\": 403.22, \"end\": 428.1, \"text\": \"in detention for longer periods while they await deportation decisions.\"}, {\"start\": 429.42, \"end\": 445.98, \"text\": \"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention says on average, 115 Americans die every day\"}, {\"start\": 445.98, \"end\": 450.26, \"text\": \"from an opioid overdose.\"}, {\"start\": 450.26, \"end\": 466.8, \"text\": \"But according to two new studies, marijuana could help curb America's opioid epidemic.\"}, {\"start\": 466.8, \"end\": 482.78, \"text\": \"Researchers compared opioid prescription patterns in states with and without medical cannabis\"}, {\"start\": 482.78, \"end\": 499.46, \"text\": \"laws and found that states with medical marijuana laws had 2.2 million fewer daily doses of\"}, {\"start\": 499.46, \"end\": 505.52, \"text\": \"opioids prescribed per year.\"}, {\"start\": 505.52, \"end\": 523.14, \"text\": \"Also opioid prescriptions under Medicaid dropped by 5.88% in states with medical marijuana.\"}, {\"start\": 523.26, \"end\": 533.16, \"text\": \"Just like opioids, marijuana has been shown to be effective in treating chronic pain and\"}, {\"start\": 533.16, \"end\": 537.52, \"text\": \"other conditions.\"}, {\"start\": 540.64, \"end\": 548.18, \"text\": \"We all know home-cooked meals are probably healthier than restaurant food.\"}, {\"start\": 548.3, \"end\": 557.32, \"text\": \"But according to a new study published in the Journal Environment International, dining\"}, {\"start\": 557.32, \"end\": 565.42, \"text\": \"out increases your exposure to potentially harmful chemicals.\"}, {\"start\": 565.42, \"end\": 577.76, \"text\": \"Those chemicals are called phthalates and researchers say they can make your hormones\"}, {\"start\": 577.76, \"end\": 580.66, \"text\": \"go haywire.\"}, {\"start\": 580.66, \"end\": 597.9, \"text\": \"The study found people who ate at restaurants and fast food outlets often had 35% higher\"}, {\"start\": 597.9, \"end\": 601.36, \"text\": \"levels of phthalates than those who didn't.\"}, {\"start\": 601.36, \"end\": 607.34, \"text\": \"Research shows that eating foods with high levels of those chemicals have been linked\"}, {\"start\": 607.34, \"end\": 610.06, \"text\": \"to birth defects.\"}, {\"start\": 610.06, \"end\": 620.42, \"text\": \"And now scientists suspect the chemicals can disrupt hormones and cause fertility problems.\"}, {\"start\": 620.42, \"end\": 625.5, \"text\": \"Researchers say the food is likely contaminated with those chemicals because it comes in contact\"}, {\"start\": 625.5, \"end\": 632.2, \"text\": \"with gloves and plastic packaging.\"}, {\"start\": 632.3, \"end\": 642.1, \"text\": \"Those same synthetic chemicals are also found in perfumes, hair sprays and shampoos.\"}, {\"start\": 642.16, \"end\": 645.6, \"text\": \"But there is good news!\"}, {\"start\": 645.6, \"end\": 652.4, \"text\": \"Those chemicals only stay in the body for about a day.\"}, {\"start\": 652.4, \"end\": 656.4, \"text\": \"So don't eliminate eating out altogether.\"}, {\"start\": 656.5, \"end\": 665.32, \"text\": \"Just try to mix in good home-cooked meals every now and again.\"}, {\"start\": 668.06, \"end\": 677.66, \"text\": \"The calendar says it's spring but some parts of the country are still getting hounded with snow.\"}, {\"start\": 677.66, \"end\": 683.34, \"text\": \"Places like Wisconsin, Minnesota and New York.\"}, {\"start\": 683.34, \"end\": 693.4, \"text\": \"In fact, Monday was the eighth most snowy April day in New York City's history.\"}, {\"start\": 693.46, \"end\": 704.5, \"text\": \"Nearly 5 inches fell in Central Park in one day.\"}, {\"start\": 704.5, \"end\": 715.56, \"text\": \"New York City usually gets about half an inch for the entire month.\"}, {\"start\": 717.84, \"end\": 720.78, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 720.78, \"end\": 722.76, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 722.76, \"end\": 726.14, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 726.14, \"end\": 732.02, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 732.06, \"end\": 739.76, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "78PYzJd_6-I": {
    "video_id": "78PYzJd_6-I",
    "title": "Weight Watchers offers teens free membership (ASL - 2.7.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180208",
    "duration": 62,
    "view_count": 94,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.76, \"end\": 13.28, \"text\": \"Weight Watchers just announced one of its goals this year: to help 10 million people\"}, {\"start\": 13.28, \"end\": 15.46, \"text\": \"adopt healthy habits.\"}, {\"start\": 15.46, \"end\": 31.08, \"text\": \"Part of that plan is to offer free memberships over the summer to teenagers 13 to 17 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 31.08, \"end\": 37.34, \"text\": \"The company also says it plans to remove all artificial ingredients from products that\"}, {\"start\": 37.34, \"end\": 40.42, \"text\": \"carry the Weight Watchers brand.\"}, {\"start\": 40.42, \"end\": 51.16, \"text\": \"Co-owner Oprah Winfrey released a statement that said: \\\"I am inspired to be part of this\"}, {\"start\": 51.16, \"end\": 55.9, \"text\": \"purpose driven mission as we deepen and expand our own connection to communities, making\"}, {\"start\": 55.9, \"end\": 61.24, \"text\": \"wellness accessible to everyone.\\\"\"}]"
  },
  "1iTycyw2jcE": {
    "video_id": "1iTycyw2jcE",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.10.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171011",
    "duration": 630,
    "view_count": 119,
    "description": "October 10, 2017\nNews for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).\n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n\n-CALIFORNIA WILDFIRES UPDATE\n-ESPN SUSPENDS JEMELE HILL\n-TWITTER PULLS BLACKBURN AD\n-BALLOONS MAY RESTORE PUERTO RICO CELL SERVICE\n-DOCKLESS BIKE-SHARING IN D.C.\n-CHRONIC BACK PAIN SURGERY ALTERNATIVES\n-GUESS NEW OREO FLAVOR & WIN $50K\n-BEARS BREAK INTO PIZZA PARLOR\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds fr",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am\"}, {\"start\": 13.0, \"end\": 16.0, \"text\": \"Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 17.0, \"end\": 20.0, \"text\": \"And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 23.0, \"end\": 28.0, \"text\": \"Wildfires continue to ravage parts of northern\"}, {\"start\": 28.0, \"end\": 32.0, \"text\": \"California. Tens of thousands of acres\"}, {\"start\": 33.0, \"end\": 36.0, \"text\": \"are on fire.\"}, {\"start\": 36.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"At least 10 people have died. Twenty-thousand\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 46.0, \"text\": \"people have evacuated and\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 51.0, \"text\": \"91-thousand don't have power.\"}, {\"start\": 52.0, \"end\": 55.0, \"text\": \"The largest fires are in\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 61.0, \"text\": \"Napa, Mendocino\"}, {\"start\": 63.0, \"end\": 68.0, \"text\": \"and Sonoma County. Authorities are telling\"}, {\"start\": 68.0, \"end\": 72.0, \"text\": \"residents to evacuate now because the\"}, {\"start\": 72.0, \"end\": 77.0, \"text\": \"flames are moving too fast. Homes and buildings\"}, {\"start\": 77.0, \"end\": 82.0, \"text\": \"have burned to the ground. In Santa\"}, {\"start\": 82.0, \"end\": 88.0, \"text\": \"Rosa entire neighborhoods are wiped out.\"}, {\"start\": 88.0, \"end\": 93.0, \"text\": \"Still some residents are trying to go\"}, {\"start\": 93.0, \"end\": 99.0, \"text\": \"back home. Officials are saying \\\"No!\\\" Stay away!\"}, {\"start\": 99.0, \"end\": 104.0, \"text\": \"It could be several days before the fires\"}, {\"start\": 105.0, \"end\": 109.0, \"text\": \"are contained. And officials need to secure\"}, {\"start\": 111.0, \"end\": 116.0, \"text\": \"power lines, gas lines and\"}, {\"start\": 116.0, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"make sure trees don't fall on someone.\"}, {\"start\": 121.0, \"end\": 126.0, \"text\": \"Today winds are expected to ease up\"}, {\"start\": 127.0, \"end\": 131.0, \"text\": \"and that will give firefighters a small\"}, {\"start\": 131.0, \"end\": 136.0, \"text\": \"break in fighting the flames.\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 144.0, \"text\": \"The federal government is offering assistance.\"}, {\"start\": 146.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"ESPN has suspended host\"}, {\"start\": 149.024, \"end\": 156.024, \"text\": \"Jemele Hill.\"}, {\"start\": 157.0, \"end\": 158.0, \"text\": \"On Sunday\"}, {\"start\": 159.0, \"end\": 163.0, \"text\": \"Hill criticized Dallas\"}, {\"start\": 163.0, \"end\": 167.0, \"text\": \"Cowboys owner Jerry\"}, {\"start\": 168.0, \"end\": 173.0, \"text\": \"Jones. Jones said any player\"}, {\"start\": 173.0, \"end\": 178.0, \"text\": \"who disrespects the flag by kneeling will not play.\"}, {\"start\": 178.0, \"end\": 182.0, \"text\": \"Hill tweeted that type of\"}, {\"start\": 183.0, \"end\": 188.0, \"text\": \"ultimatum puts an unfair burden on players.\"}, {\"start\": 188.0, \"end\": 192.0, \"text\": \"She encouraged people who disagree with Jones\"}, {\"start\": 193.0, \"end\": 197.0, \"text\": \"to put pressure on\"}, {\"start\": 197.0, \"end\": 201.0, \"text\": \"his advertisers.\"}, {\"start\": 201.0, \"end\": 207.0, \"text\": \"ESPN suspended Hill for two weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 208.0, \"end\": 212.0, \"text\": \"The network said Hill has\"}, {\"start\": 212.0, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"now violated its social media guidelines\"}, {\"start\": 217.0, \"end\": 222.0, \"text\": \"not once but twice.\"}, {\"start\": 222.0, \"end\": 227.0, \"text\": \"If you recall a few weeks ago Hill tweeted\"}, {\"start\": 227.0, \"end\": 233.0, \"text\": \"President Trump was a white supremacist.\"}, {\"start\": 235.0, \"end\": 239.0, \"text\": \"Twitter has stopped a\"}, {\"start\": 240.0, \"end\": 244.0, \"text\": \"Tennessee Senate candidate from\"}, {\"start\": 245.0, \"end\": 249.0, \"text\": \"advertising on its site. The company says\"}, {\"start\": 250.0, \"end\": 255.0, \"text\": \"Congresswoman Marsha Blackburn's\"}, {\"start\": 255.0, \"end\": 259.0, \"text\": \"campaign announcement video is\"}, {\"start\": 260.0, \"end\": 265.0, \"text\": \"inflammatory. Blackburn\"}, {\"start\": 265.0, \"end\": 270.0, \"text\": \"is running to fill the seat of retiring\"}, {\"start\": 270.0, \"end\": 276.0, \"text\": \"Senator Bob Corker.\"}, {\"start\": 276.0, \"end\": 280.0, \"text\": \"In her campaign video Blackburn says:\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 285.0, \"text\": \"\\\" I fought Planned Parenthood\"}, {\"start\": 286.0, \"end\": 290.0, \"text\": \"and we stopped the sale of baby parts.\"}, {\"start\": 292.0, \"end\": 297.0, \"text\": \"Thank God.\\\" The ad is still posted\"}, {\"start\": 297.0, \"end\": 303.0, \"text\": \"but Blackburn's campaign is not allowed to pay\"}, {\"start\": 303.024, \"end\": 305.024, \"text\": \"to advertise it.\"}, {\"start\": 308.0, \"end\": 311.0, \"text\": \"Millions of people in Puerto Rico are still\"}, {\"start\": 311.001, \"end\": 313.003, \"text\": \"without cell service\"}, {\"start\": 313.5, \"end\": 316.5, \"text\": \"after Hurricane Maria devastated the island.\"}, {\"start\": 317.0, \"end\": 321.0, \"text\": \"But giant balloons like this\"}, {\"start\": 321.0, \"end\": 323.0, \"text\": \"might be the answer to the problem.\"}, {\"start\": 325.001, \"end\": 329.299, \"text\": \"The Federal Communications Commission\"}, {\"start\": 330.5, \"end\": 334.0, \"text\": \"has approved Project Loon.\"}, {\"start\": 334.0, \"end\": 338.0, \"text\": \"It uses balloons to help provide Internet\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 344.0, \"text\": \"service to people in hard to reach places.\"}, {\"start\": 344.1, \"end\": 349.1, \"text\": \"People in Puerto Rico could possibly get a cell signal by\"}, {\"start\": 349.1, \"end\": 353.1, \"text\": \"connecting their phones to the balloons. But first\"}, {\"start\": 353.1, \"end\": 359.1, \"text\": \"Project Loon needs to partner with a phone service provider.\"}, {\"start\": 360.0, \"end\": 367.0, \"text\": \"The balloons can't do anything until that happens.\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 373.0, \"text\": \"If you live in Washington D.C. you may have seen a few of these around town.\"}, {\"start\": 373.0, \"end\": 378.0, \"text\": \"you may have seen a few of these around town. It's a dockless\"}, {\"start\": 378.0, \"end\": 383.0, \"text\": \"bike and it's part of a six-month bike sharing trial program.\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 388.0, \"text\": \"The program launched today. The city is looking at whether\"}, {\"start\": 388.0, \"end\": 393.0, \"text\": \"bike sharing should become a permanent transportation option in\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 399.0, \"text\": \"the nation's capitol. These bikes don't have to be returned to a home base.\"}, {\"start\": 399.0, \"end\": 403.0, \"text\": \"These bikes are tracked and locked using the bike company's\"}, {\"start\": 403.0, \"end\": 409.0, \"text\": \"smartphone app.\"}, {\"start\": 409.1, \"end\": 417.1, \"text\": \"Riders pay a dollar an hour to use them.\"}, {\"start\": 422.024, \"end\": 423.899, \"text\": \"Chronic back pain can be debilitating\"}, {\"start\": 424.0, \"end\": 428.0, \"text\": \"for many people. Many people are choosing surgery\"}, {\"start\": 428.0, \"end\": 433.0, \"text\": \"to relieve the pain. But some doctors say\"}, {\"start\": 433.0, \"end\": 438.0, \"text\": \"there are many ways to relieve the pain without going under the knife.\"}, {\"start\": 438.0, \"end\": 442.0, \"text\": \"Physical therapy is an option.\"}, {\"start\": 443.0, \"end\": 447.0, \"text\": \"People learn better posture, gain flexibility and\"}, {\"start\": 447.0, \"end\": 451.0, \"text\": \"core strength -- all of which helps their condition improve.\"}, {\"start\": 452.0, \"end\": 457.0, \"text\": \"Yoga and meditation is another option. It can help\"}, {\"start\": 457.0, \"end\": 460.0, \"text\": \"fight the emotional turmoil.\"}, {\"start\": 460.0, \"end\": 465.0, \"text\": \"Mindful exercise can train the brain to not focus\"}, {\"start\": 465.0, \"end\": 470.0, \"text\": \"on the physical discomfort. Changes in your\"}, {\"start\": 470.0, \"end\": 477.0, \"text\": \"diet and other lifestyle modifications can also help relieve back pain.\"}, {\"start\": 479.8, \"end\": 487.8, \"text\": \"Massage and acupuncture also help.\"}, {\"start\": 488.0, \"end\": 493.0, \"text\": \"And give up smoking. Doctors say\"}, {\"start\": 494.0, \"end\": 499.0, \"text\": \"nicotine has been known to make pain worse.\"}, {\"start\": 499.0, \"end\": 503.0, \"text\": \"These tips may help you avoid surgery\"}, {\"start\": 503.0, \"end\": 507.0, \"text\": \"but always remember to discuss any health decisions\"}, {\"start\": 508.0, \"end\": 513.0, \"text\": \"with your doctor first.\"}, {\"start\": 516.0, \"end\": 520.0, \"text\": \"Oreo is offering a sweet prize. Anyone who\"}, {\"start\": 522.0, \"end\": 527.0, \"text\": \"can figure out the limited-edition\"}, {\"start\": 527.0, \"end\": 532.0, \"text\": \"mystery flavor could win $50,000.\"}, {\"start\": 532.0, \"end\": 536.0, \"text\": \"Those who guessed the correct flavor\"}, {\"start\": 536.0, \"end\": 542.0, \"text\": \"through November 30th will be considered for the prize.\"}, {\"start\": 542.0, \"end\": 547.0, \"text\": \"Five 10-thousand dollar prizes are also being offered.\"}, {\"start\": 549.001, \"end\": 551.499, \"text\": \"You're only allowed one guess\"}, {\"start\": 551.6, \"end\": 555.6, \"text\": \"each day during the contest period.\"}, {\"start\": 555.6, \"end\": 558.0, \"text\": \"For more information\"}, {\"start\": 558.0, \"end\": 563.0, \"text\": \"go to oreomystery.com.\"}, {\"start\": 566.0, \"end\": 568.0, \"text\": \"Check out this video.\"}, {\"start\": 568.0, \"end\": 573.0, \"text\": \"In Colorado a mother bear and her two cubs\"}, {\"start\": 573.0, \"end\": 578.0, \"text\": \"break into a pizza restaurant and they eat everything they can get their paws on.\"}, {\"start\": 578.0, \"end\": 583.0, \"text\": \"When the owners came in the next day they thought\"}, {\"start\": 584.0, \"end\": 587.0, \"text\": \"they had been robbed by humans.\"}, {\"start\": 589.0, \"end\": 593.0, \"text\": \"But after looking at the security video they found out the real thieves were bear bandits.\"}, {\"start\": 594.0, \"end\": 600.0, \"text\": \"After some repairs and tidying up the business reopened.\"}, {\"start\": 602.0, \"end\": 606.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 606.0, \"end\": 609.0, \"text\": \"I am Jethro Wooddall. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 610.0, \"end\": 614.0, \"text\": \"And remember to \\\"Like\\\" us on Facebook.\"}, {\"start\": 614.024, \"end\": 621.024, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "c1KAO1PjIrI": {
    "video_id": "c1KAO1PjIrI",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.7.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180407",
    "duration": 402,
    "view_count": 1316,
    "description": "4.7.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-UFC star Conor McGregor charged with assault\n-National Guard troops deploy to border\n-Oklahoma teachers seeing action from lawmakers\n-Best Buy hit by same data breach as Sears, Delta\n-Russell Crowe hosts divorce auction\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY,",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.44, \"end\": 8.66, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.66, \"end\": 11.04, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.04, \"end\": 13.02, \"text\": \"I’m Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 13.02, \"end\": 16.08, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.96, \"end\": 31.66, \"text\": \"Ultimate Fighting champion Conor McGregor appeared before a New York City judge Friday\"}, {\"start\": 31.66, \"end\": 36.4, \"text\": \"to answer for his alleged attack the night before.\"}, {\"start\": 36.4, \"end\": 44.23, \"text\": \"Police say McGregor and his large entourage went to the loading docks of the Barclay’s\"}, {\"start\": 44.23, \"end\": 51.64, \"text\": \"Center where other UFC fighters were getting onto buses.\"}, {\"start\": 51.64, \"end\": 61.84, \"text\": \"McGregor allegedly had an issue with one of the men slated to compete for the lightweight title.\"}, {\"start\": 61.84, \"end\": 66.98, \"text\": \"McGregor held that title until he was stripped of it this week.\"}, {\"start\": 66.98, \"end\": 78.1, \"text\": \"Witnesses say McGregor chased down the bus and threw a dolly at it, smashing a window.\"}, {\"start\": 78.1, \"end\": 83.36, \"text\": \"The entire incident was caught on cell phone video.\"}, {\"start\": 100.62, \"end\": 108.96, \"text\": \"Two fighters were hurt in the attack and were forced to withdraw from tonight’s UFC event.\"}, {\"start\": 108.96, \"end\": 115.76, \"text\": \"Now UFC’s president is questioning whether McGregor is good for the sport.\"}, {\"start\": 119.24, \"end\": 126.92, \"text\": \"Earlier this week we told you about President Trump signing a memorandum to deploy the National\"}, {\"start\": 126.92, \"end\": 129.4, \"text\": \"Guard to the southern border.\"}, {\"start\": 129.4, \"end\": 134.14, \"text\": \"The deployment has started.\"}, {\"start\": 134.14, \"end\": 140.26, \"text\": \"This is video of the helicopters taking off for the US/Mexico border.\"}, {\"start\": 140.26, \"end\": 148.72, \"text\": \"Texas plans to send 150 National guardsmen this weekend and Arizona is planning to send\"}, {\"start\": 148.72, \"end\": 151.04, \"text\": \"150 guardsmen next week.\"}, {\"start\": 151.04, \"end\": 161.88, \"text\": \"The guards will provide air support, operational support and construction of border infrastructure.\"}, {\"start\": 161.88, \"end\": 167.14, \"text\": \"Governors in California and New Mexico have not said whether they will participate in\"}, {\"start\": 167.14, \"end\": 169.96, \"text\": \"the border security mission.\"}, {\"start\": 172.32, \"end\": 183.06, \"text\": \"Oklahoma teachers are seeing action from lawmakers for the fifth day of their statewide strike.\"}, {\"start\": 183.06, \"end\": 194.74, \"text\": \"The state Senate passed a bill Friday to tax sales from Amazon and other internet retailers.\"}, {\"start\": 194.74, \"end\": 202.56, \"text\": \"The move is expected to provide an extra $20 million in education funding.\"}, {\"start\": 202.56, \"end\": 210.68, \"text\": \"Teachers are also pushing lawmakers to pass a separate tax bill on gambling.\"}, {\"start\": 210.68, \"end\": 216.29, \"text\": \"But there’s no word yet on the fate of that bill.\"}, {\"start\": 216.29, \"end\": 224.3, \"text\": \"Teachers have been at the state capitol since Monday, demanding better paychecks and more\"}, {\"start\": 224.3, \"end\": 227.44, \"text\": \"money for education.\"}, {\"start\": 227.44, \"end\": 235.72, \"text\": \"The teachers recently got $6,000 raises and $50 million in extra education money.\"}, {\"start\": 235.72, \"end\": 241.84, \"text\": \"But the teachers say those changes are not enough.\"}, {\"start\": 244.0, \"end\": 253.44, \"text\": \"On Friday Best Buy said that some of its customers’ credit card information may have been impacted\"}, {\"start\": 253.44, \"end\": 256.88, \"text\": \"by a data breach.\"}, {\"start\": 256.88, \"end\": 263.38, \"text\": \"This is the same breach that Sears and Delta Airlines have already reported to be victims of.\"}, {\"start\": 263.38, \"end\": 273.68, \"text\": \"The three companies all use “24-7.ai,” a third-party firm that provides online and\"}, {\"start\": 273.68, \"end\": 276.88, \"text\": \"mobile chat services to customers.\"}, {\"start\": 276.88, \"end\": 285.44, \"text\": \"That firm reveals it had an illegal intrusion between September 27 and October 12 of last year.\"}, {\"start\": 285.44, \"end\": 291.76, \"text\": \"Best Buy says it appears only a small fraction of its customers might have been affected.\"}, {\"start\": 291.76, \"end\": 297.28, \"text\": \"Sears says less than 10,000 of its customers were exposed.\"}, {\"start\": 297.28, \"end\": 304.24, \"text\": \"Delta could not determine how many.\"}, {\"start\": 306.56, \"end\": 322.24, \"text\": \"In 2012 actor Russell Crowe and his wife Danielle Spencer ended their nine year marriage.\"}, {\"start\": 322.24, \"end\": 331.68, \"text\": \"Today in Sydney, Australia, Crowe threw a divorce auction party and sold mementos from\"}, {\"start\": 331.68, \"end\": 335.68, \"text\": \"that marriage.\"}, {\"start\": 335.68, \"end\": 339.52, \"text\": \"Today also happens to be his birthday and wedding anniversary.\"}, {\"start\": 339.52, \"end\": 351.68, \"text\": \"Hundreds of items were up for grabs: art, watches, diamond rings and his Mercedes-Benz.\"}, {\"start\": 351.68, \"end\": 361.44, \"text\": \"He even auctioned off a pair of satin boxers and his leather jockstrap.\"}, {\"start\": 361.44, \"end\": 371.04, \"text\": \"Each item comes with the description of their role in Crowe’s personal and movie life.\"}, {\"start\": 373.28, \"end\": 375.48, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 375.52, \"end\": 377.68, \"text\": \"I’m Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 377.68, \"end\": 380.4, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 380.4, \"end\": 386.56, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 386.56, \"end\": 388.72, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 388.72, \"end\": 390.32, \"text\": \"Your Life.\"}, {\"start\": 390.4, \"end\": 393.76, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-zsVFWyuQ1g": {
    "video_id": "-zsVFWyuQ1g",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.8.19 - News for the Deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20191009",
    "duration": 551,
    "view_count": 1453,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n\n- FBI needs help identifying victims of serial killer\n- Girl with cerebral palsy takes first steps \n- House Dems to subpoena ambassador Sondland\n- Dick's destroys $5 million worth of assault rifles\n- Owning a dog helps you live longer\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 24.64, \"end\": 25.92, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 25.92, \"end\": 28.44, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 28.44, \"end\": 29.76, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 29.76, \"end\": 32.64, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 34.4, \"end\": 40.64, \"text\": \"The FBI is asking for help solving the crimes of a man they say is responsible for more\"}, {\"start\": 40.64, \"end\": 46.0, \"text\": \"deaths than any other serial killer.\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 60.08, \"text\": \"Last year, 79-year-old Samuel Little confessed to strangling 93 victims between 1970 and\"}, {\"start\": 60.08, \"end\": 62.38, \"text\": \"2005.\"}, {\"start\": 62.4, \"end\": 67.12, \"text\": \"Little often targeted women of vulnerable groups, many who were involved in prostitution\"}, {\"start\": 67.12, \"end\": 70.16, \"text\": \"or suffering from a drug addiction.\"}, {\"start\": 70.16, \"end\": 78.24, \"text\": \"Little was convicted in 2014 and is now serving three life sentences in California.\"}, {\"start\": 78.24, \"end\": 88.96, \"text\": \"Law enforcement so far has verified 50 of the confessions, but want the public's help\"}, {\"start\": 88.96, \"end\": 92.24, \"text\": \"in dozens of other cases.\"}, {\"start\": 92.24, \"end\": 99.42, \"text\": \"The FBI says that the bodies sometimes went unidentified, and the death never investigated.\"}, {\"start\": 99.44, \"end\": 104.52, \"text\": \"They've released information about five cases on the agency's website.\"}, {\"start\": 104.52, \"end\": 113.6, \"text\": \"Authorities are hoping that someone may remember a detail that could further the investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 113.6, \"end\": 122.4, \"text\": \"Each case presented is accompanied by video of Little explaining the incident and a hand-drawn\"}, {\"start\": 122.4, \"end\": 125.38, \"text\": \"photo by Little of the woman.\"}, {\"start\": 125.38, \"end\": 132.48, \"text\": \"The FBI believes all of his recollections are credible.\"}, {\"start\": 132.48, \"end\": 139.68, \"text\": \"Little did not seem to express any remorse in his confessions.\"}, {\"start\": 143.84, \"end\": 153.24, \"text\": \"A proud Texas mom shared this video of her daughter's huge accomplishment with the world.\"}, {\"start\": 153.24, \"end\": 165.8, \"text\": \"It shows her six-year-old Love Johnson taking her first unaided steps.\"}, {\"start\": 165.8, \"end\": 175.76, \"text\": \"Love has cerebral palsy and has never walked on her own.\"}, {\"start\": 175.76, \"end\": 181.6, \"text\": \"Just last year, she was given a wheelchair and a walker.\"}, {\"start\": 181.6, \"end\": 190.4, \"text\": \"Her mother, Lovely Johnson posted this video on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 190.4, \"end\": 200.16, \"text\": \"As you can see, the child takes her steps without assistance from a walker or braces.\"}, {\"start\": 200.16, \"end\": 204.72, \"text\": \"Johnson says her daughter is her hero.\"}, {\"start\": 209.44, \"end\": 215.2, \"text\": \"As part of their impeachment inquiry, House Democrats say they will now subpoena U.S.\"}, {\"start\": 215.2, \"end\": 227.12, \"text\": \"Ambassador to the European Union Gordon Sondland to testify.\"}, {\"start\": 227.12, \"end\": 235.36, \"text\": \"Tuesday the White House blocked the key witness from testifying before Congress in the Democrat's\"}, {\"start\": 235.36, \"end\": 238.72, \"text\": \"impeachment probe.\"}, {\"start\": 238.72, \"end\": 249.24, \"text\": \"Sondland was scheduled to testify before three House committees in a closed-door meeting.\"}, {\"start\": 249.24, \"end\": 255.66, \"text\": \"Sondland was involved in text messages turned over to the House Intelligence Committee last\"}, {\"start\": 255.68, \"end\": 262.82, \"text\": \"week regarding the Ukraine controversy.\"}, {\"start\": 262.82, \"end\": 272.72, \"text\": \"The messages show how a potential Ukrainian investigation into the 2016 election was linked\"}, {\"start\": 272.72, \"end\": 281.28, \"text\": \"to a desired meeting between Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky and President Donald Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 281.28, \"end\": 294.96, \"text\": \"Sondland was also mentioned in the whistleblower complaint for allegedly giving advice to Ukrainian\"}, {\"start\": 294.96, \"end\": 303.24, \"text\": \"leadership about navigating demands Trump made of Zelensky.\"}, {\"start\": 303.24, \"end\": 308.42, \"text\": \"Meanwhile, extreme measures are being considered to protect the identity and safety of the\"}, {\"start\": 308.42, \"end\": 310.2, \"text\": \"whistleblower.\"}, {\"start\": 310.2, \"end\": 317.44, \"text\": \"It's still not clear if the whistleblower will end up talking to the House Intelligence Committee.\"}, {\"start\": 317.44, \"end\": 324.32, \"text\": \"But in the case that does happen, measures being discussed include using an off-site\"}, {\"start\": 324.32, \"end\": 331.82, \"text\": \"location, limiting House Intelligence staff and members who would be present and disguising\"}, {\"start\": 331.84, \"end\": 333.92, \"text\": \"the individual's image and voice.\"}, {\"start\": 337.84, \"end\": 351.12, \"text\": \"Dick's Sporting Goods has destroyed more than five-million dollars worth of assault rifles.\"}, {\"start\": 351.12, \"end\": 358.94, \"text\": \"That's according to CEO Ed Stack who made the announcement in an interview with CBS News.\"}, {\"start\": 358.96, \"end\": 366.54, \"text\": \"He said the company turned the weapons into scrap metal.\"}, {\"start\": 366.54, \"end\": 372.78, \"text\": \"The move comes after Dick's made the decision last year to stop carrying the rifles following\"}, {\"start\": 372.8, \"end\": 378.02, \"text\": \"the mass shooting in Parkland, Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 378.02, \"end\": 381.64, \"text\": \"The shooting left 17 people dead.\"}, {\"start\": 381.64, \"end\": 387.04, \"text\": \"The company sold the shooter a shotgun.\"}, {\"start\": 387.04, \"end\": 396.32, \"text\": \"Even though it wasn't the weapon used in the shooting, that largely impacted the company's actions.\"}, {\"start\": 396.32, \"end\": 406.8, \"text\": \"Dick's also said it would stop selling high capacity magazines and raised its gun purchasing\"}, {\"start\": 406.8, \"end\": 410.1, \"text\": \"age to 21 from 18.\"}, {\"start\": 410.1, \"end\": 417.8, \"text\": \"Stacks said in the CBS interview that the changes cost the company nearly a quarter\"}, {\"start\": 417.8, \"end\": 421.2, \"text\": \"billion dollars in sales.\"}, {\"start\": 421.2, \"end\": 430.48, \"text\": \"Other stores are also grappling with gun sales following mass shootings across the country.\"}, {\"start\": 430.48, \"end\": 438.96, \"text\": \"Walmart announced last month that it would reduce its gun and ammunition sales.\"}, {\"start\": 438.96, \"end\": 453.12, \"text\": \"The store also asked customers to stop carrying weapons openly in stores, even in open carry states.\"}, {\"start\": 457.68, \"end\": 468.64, \"text\": \"According to new research from the University of Toronto, dogs could add years to your life.\"}, {\"start\": 468.64, \"end\": 476.16, \"text\": \"Researchers analyzed data from four million people in six countries.\"}, {\"start\": 476.16, \"end\": 484.28, \"text\": \"They found dog owners had a lower risk of dying early by 24-percent.\"}, {\"start\": 484.28, \"end\": 491.04, \"text\": \"For those who already had a heart attack, the risk of dying was lowered by 31-percent.\"}, {\"start\": 491.04, \"end\": 498.16, \"text\": \"A major factor could be pet owners who walk their dogs got up to 30 minutes of exercise\"}, {\"start\": 498.16, \"end\": 500.84, \"text\": \"a day.\"}, {\"start\": 500.84, \"end\": 513.2, \"text\": \"Studies also show petting dogs can reduce blood pressure, anxiety and depression.\"}, {\"start\": 516.64, \"end\": 519.2, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 519.2, \"end\": 521.04, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 521.04, \"end\": 524.38, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 524.38, \"end\": 534.16, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our\"}, {\"start\": 534.16, \"end\": 536.32, \"text\": \"app too.\"}, {\"start\": 536.32, \"end\": 538.08, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 538.08, \"end\": 539.88, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 539.88, \"end\": 542.46, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "y_sYQK0SE6A": {
    "video_id": "y_sYQK0SE6A",
    "title": "October 2, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171003",
    "duration": 512,
    "view_count": 272,
    "description": "October 2, 2017\nNews for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).\n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n\n-LAS VEGAS SHOOTING\n-WITNESS SHOWS BLOOD ON LEGS\n-WHO WAS THE LAS VEGAS SHOOTER?\n-MAP OF LAS VEGAS STRIP\n-EXTERIOR OF MANDALAY BAY HOTEL\n-WHITE HOUSE MOMENT OF SILENCE\n-JASON ALDEAN SPEAKS OUT\n-PHONE NUMBER TO FIND MISSING LOVED ONES\n-LONG LINES TO DONATE BLOOD\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from not",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 13.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 13.0, \"end\": 16.0, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau\"}, {\"start\": 18.0, \"end\": 21.0, \"text\": \"and here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 25.0, \"end\": 29.0, \"text\": \"We start with the worst mass shooting incident\"}, {\"start\": 31.0, \"end\": 36.0, \"text\": \"in recent U.S. history. Last night in Las Vegas\"}, {\"start\": 37.0, \"end\": 42.0, \"text\": \"about 30,000 people  gathered to watch a\"}, {\"start\": 42.0, \"end\": 45.0, \"text\": \"concert.\"}, {\"start\": 45.0, \"end\": 49.0, \"text\": \"They were there to see country music star\"}, {\"start\": 51.0, \"end\": 56.0, \"text\": \"Jason Aldean. During the concert someone on the\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 61.0, \"text\": \"32nd floor of the building across the\"}, {\"start\": 61.0, \"end\": 67.0, \"text\": \"street, at Mandalay Bay Hotel,\"}, {\"start\": 70.0, \"end\": 75.0, \"text\": \"started shooting at the people below. At first\"}, {\"start\": 76.0, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"people thought it was fireworks. But when they realized\"}, {\"start\": 81.0, \"end\": 86.0, \"text\": \"someone was shooting at them they started running for cover.\"}, {\"start\": 86.0, \"end\": 91.0, \"text\": \"It was complete chaos. Bodies were all over the ground.\"}, {\"start\": 91.0, \"end\": 95.0, \"text\": \"Many were dead. As of right now 58 people are\"}, {\"start\": 95.0, \"end\": 100.0, \"text\": \"dead. Five hundred fifteen are injured but\"}, {\"start\": 100.0, \"end\": 108.0, \"text\": \"those numbers are expected to climb.\"}, {\"start\": 108.0, \"end\": 112.0, \"text\": \"The woman in this video was at the concert\"}, {\"start\": 114.0, \"end\": 119.0, \"text\": \"and she is covered in blood. But it is not her\"}, {\"start\": 119.0, \"end\": 123.0, \"text\": \"blood. She said when the shooting started\"}, {\"start\": 123.0, \"end\": 128.0, \"text\": \"blood splattered everywhere. Some people\"}, {\"start\": 128.0, \"end\": 133.0, \"text\": \"ran. Others ducked down trying to seek\"}, {\"start\": 133.0, \"end\": 138.0, \"text\": \"cover. Bodies were falling left and right.\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 143.0, \"text\": \"Some people landed on people who were dead.\"}, {\"start\": 143.0, \"end\": 145.0, \"text\": \"Others landed on people who were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 151.0, \"end\": 156.0, \"text\": \"Police say this man was the shooter. His name was\"}, {\"start\": 156.0, \"end\": 161.0, \"text\": \"Stephen Paddock. He was 64 years old. He's dead now.\"}, {\"start\": 161.0, \"end\": 165.0, \"text\": \"Officials say when police confronted him in the hotel\"}, {\"start\": 168.0, \"end\": 173.0, \"text\": \"he killed himself. Police say Paddock\"}, {\"start\": 173.0, \"end\": 178.0, \"text\": \"lived in the Las Vegas area.\"}, {\"start\": 178.0, \"end\": 182.0, \"text\": \"He was a retired accountant. His brother\"}, {\"start\": 182.0, \"end\": 187.0, \"text\": \"says he didn't have any connections with hate\"}, {\"start\": 187.0, \"end\": 192.0, \"text\": \"groups or terrorist groups. He says\"}, {\"start\": 192.0, \"end\": 197.0, \"text\": \"his brother did not have an arrest record nor did\"}, {\"start\": 197.0, \"end\": 202.0, \"text\": \"he have mental illness issues. He\"}, {\"start\": 202.0, \"end\": 208.0, \"text\": \"has no idea why Paddock would do something like this.\"}, {\"start\": 214.0, \"end\": 216.0, \"text\": \"Here is a map of where the shooting took place.\"}, {\"start\": 219.0, \"end\": 224.0, \"text\": \"The shooting happened on the Las Vegas strip\"}, {\"start\": 224.0, \"end\": 230.0, \"text\": \"marked by the red line.\"}, {\"start\": 230.0, \"end\": 235.0, \"text\": \"You can also see in red the Mandalay Bay Hotel where the shooting took\"}, {\"start\": 235.0, \"end\": 238.0, \"text\": \"place. Just across from the hotel\"}, {\"start\": 240.0, \"end\": 246.0, \"text\": \"is where the concert took place.\"}, {\"start\": 246.0, \"end\": 251.0, \"text\": \"This is video of the outside of Mandalay\"}, {\"start\": 251.0, \"end\": 252.0, \"text\": \"Bay Hotel. You can see the two\"}, {\"start\": 257.0, \"end\": 262.0, \"text\": \"windows on the 32nd floor have been broken out.\"}, {\"start\": 262.0, \"end\": 267.0, \"text\": \"Police believe the shooter Stephen Paddock\"}, {\"start\": 270.0, \"end\": 274.0, \"text\": \"used something like a hammer to smash out the windows\"}, {\"start\": 277.0, \"end\": 280.0, \"text\": \"and then  started shooting at the people below.\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"Today on the White House front lawn\"}, {\"start\": 289.0, \"end\": 294.0, \"text\": \"President Trump, his wife First Lady\"}, {\"start\": 294.0, \"end\": 299.0, \"text\": \"Melania Trump and the\"}, {\"start\": 299.0, \"end\": 304.0, \"text\": \"entire White House staff held a\"}, {\"start\": 304.0, \"end\": 308.0, \"text\": \"moment of silence for the Las Vegas victims.\"}, {\"start\": 313.0, \"end\": 317.0, \"text\": \"The President ordered all flags on\"}, {\"start\": 317.0, \"end\": 320.0, \"text\": \"federal buildings to be flown at half staff.\"}, {\"start\": 323.0, \"end\": 327.0, \"text\": \"President Trump said the shooting\"}, {\"start\": 328.0, \"end\": 333.0, \"text\": \"was an act of pure evil. The\"}, {\"start\": 333.0, \"end\": 338.0, \"text\": \"President offered his warmest condolences and sympathies\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 341.0, \"text\": \"to the victims and their families.\"}, {\"start\": 350.0, \"end\": 352.0, \"text\": \"Singer Jason Aldean wrote on Instagram:\"}, {\"start\": 358.0, \"end\": 363.0, \"text\": \"Tonight was beyond horrific. I still don't know what to say.\"}, {\"start\": 363.0, \"end\": 368.0, \"text\": \"But I wanted to let everyone know that\"}, {\"start\": 368.0, \"end\": 371.0, \"text\": \"me and my crew are safe.\"}, {\"start\": 371.0, \"end\": 377.0, \"text\": \"My thoughts and prayers go out to everyone involved tonight.\"}, {\"start\": 377.0, \"end\": 382.0, \"text\": \"It hurts my heart that this would happen to anyone\"}, {\"start\": 382.0, \"end\": 386.0, \"text\": \"who was just coming out to enjoy what should have been a fun night.\"}, {\"start\": 393.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"If you had family or friends who were at the\"}, {\"start\": 398.0, \"end\": 402.0, \"text\": \"Jason Aldean concert but you cannot contact\"}, {\"start\": 402.0, \"end\": 407.0, \"text\": \"them, here is a number you can call for\"}, {\"start\": 407.0, \"end\": 410.0, \"text\": \"more information. It was tweeted by\"}, {\"start\": 410.0, \"end\": 419.0, \"text\": \"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell.\"}, {\"start\": 420.0, \"end\": 425.0, \"text\": \"The number is 1-866-535-5654\"}, {\"start\": 431.0, \"end\": 436.0, \"text\": \"Immediately after the shooting people\"}, {\"start\": 436.0, \"end\": 444.0, \"text\": \"started lining up to donate blood.\"}, {\"start\": 444.0, \"end\": 448.0, \"text\": \"Police say with so many victims, there is a\"}, {\"start\": 450.0, \"end\": 455.0, \"text\": \"desperate need for blood. If you live in the Las\"}, {\"start\": 455.0, \"end\": 463.0, \"text\": \"Vegas area you can go to two locations to donate.\"}, {\"start\": 463.0, \"end\": 473.0, \"text\": \"The first is 6930 West Charleston\"}, {\"start\": 473.0, \"end\": 477.0, \"text\": \"in Las Vegas. The second is 601\"}, {\"start\": 477.0, \"end\": 485.0, \"text\": \"Whitney Ranch in Henderson Nevada.\"}, {\"start\": 488.0, \"end\": 492.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories today. I am\"}, {\"start\": 492.0, \"end\": 497.0, \"text\": \"Crystal Cousineau. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 498.0, \"end\": 503.0, \"text\": \"Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "SBSHrSnP7G8": {
    "video_id": "SBSHrSnP7G8",
    "title": "Sign1News 7.11.20",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200711",
    "duration": 893,
    "view_count": 1395,
    "description": "Sign1News, a leading deaf news source, uses American Sign Language to cover the top news stories of the week.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.46, \"end\": 9.7, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.7, \"end\": 13.32, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 13.38, \"end\": 15.36, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 15.36, \"end\": 17.36, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 23.36, \"end\": 31.8, \"text\": \"The number of new reported coronavirus cases continues to shatter records across the country.\"}, {\"start\": 31.9, \"end\": 40.66, \"text\": \"In fact on Thursday there were 63,000 new coronavirus cases, a new single day record.\"}, {\"start\": 40.66, \"end\": 48.14, \"text\": \"Death rates have surged in at least 10 states.\"}, {\"start\": 48.14, \"end\": 55.08, \"text\": \"Texas's governor extended the state's disaster declaration.\"}, {\"start\": 55.08, \"end\": 69.54, \"text\": \"The morgue in Nueces County has now hit capacity and an infant is one of the latest victims\"}, {\"start\": 69.54, \"end\": 72.04, \"text\": \"of the virus.\"}, {\"start\": 72.04, \"end\": 81.2, \"text\": \"Officials with San Antonio Methodist Hospital say a 30-year-old man was killed by the virus\"}, {\"start\": 81.2, \"end\": 85.72, \"text\": \"after attending a Covid party.\"}, {\"start\": 85.72, \"end\": 94.72, \"text\": \"Before he died the man told nurses he made a mistake by thinking the disease was a hoax\"}, {\"start\": 95.04, \"end\": 101.8, \"text\": \"and because he was young he would not be affected by the disease.\"}, {\"start\": 101.8, \"end\": 114.48, \"text\": \"On Friday Georgia, Illinois and Utah reported a record high cases.\"}, {\"start\": 114.48, \"end\": 122.4, \"text\": \"California alone surpassed 300,000 cases.\"}, {\"start\": 122.4, \"end\": 132.28, \"text\": \"West Virginia now has the highest rate of transmission in the country.\"}, {\"start\": 132.28, \"end\": 142.48, \"text\": \"And for the second time in Florida more than 11,000 new cases were reported in a single day.\"}, {\"start\": 142.48, \"end\": 155.0, \"text\": \"Florida is averaging more than 9,000 cases a day, up more than 1,200% since the state\"}, {\"start\": 155.16, \"end\": 159.72, \"text\": \"started reopening in May.\"}, {\"start\": 159.72, \"end\": 168.28, \"text\": \"Now the World Health Organization is warning that \\\"in our current situation, it is very\"}, {\"start\": 168.28, \"end\": 171.2, \"text\": \"unlikely that we can eradicate or eliminate the virus.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 174.76, \"end\": 181.48, \"text\": \"Here's a quick look at coronavirus around the globe.\"}, {\"start\": 181.48, \"end\": 195.48, \"text\": \"According to Johns Hopkins University, Latin America and Caribbean countries surpassed\"}, {\"start\": 195.48, \"end\": 204.2, \"text\": \"3 million Covid 19 cases this week.\"}, {\"start\": 204.2, \"end\": 215.6, \"text\": \"Brazil, Peru and Chile reported the highest numbers of infections.\"}, {\"start\": 215.6, \"end\": 222.68, \"text\": \"More than 50% of the cases in the Americas are being registered in the Latin America\"}, {\"start\": 222.84, \"end\": 225.0, \"text\": \"and Caribbean region.\"}, {\"start\": 225.0, \"end\": 232.52, \"text\": \"Brazil alone is  accounts for nearly 1/4 of the cases.\"}, {\"start\": 232.52, \"end\": 237.48, \"text\": \"Italy is likely to extend the state of emergency in the country due to the continued effects\"}, {\"start\": 237.48, \"end\": 241.08, \"text\": \"of the coronavirus outbreak.\"}, {\"start\": 241.08, \"end\": 249.36, \"text\": \"Reports have emerged suggesting the government will aim to extend the state of emergency\"}, {\"start\": 249.36, \"end\": 252.24, \"text\": \"until December 31.\"}, {\"start\": 252.24, \"end\": 261.48, \"text\": \"The legal guidelines behind the state of emergency grants the government special powers like\"}, {\"start\": 261.52, \"end\": 267.84, \"text\": \"allowing it to curb certain freedoms as well as permitting access to additional resources\"}, {\"start\": 267.84, \"end\": 274.34, \"text\": \"to stop and contain the spread of Covid 19.\"}, {\"start\": 274.34, \"end\": 281.38, \"text\": \"The current state of emergency is set to expire on July 31.\"}, {\"start\": 281.38, \"end\": 293.52, \"text\": \"Despite a surge in Japan's coronavirus cases, restrictions are easing.\"}, {\"start\": 293.52, \"end\": 303.08, \"text\": \"Japanese baseball is being played in a stadium in front of fans for the first time in four months.\"}, {\"start\": 303.08, \"end\": 314.64, \"text\": \"But there is a long list of \\\"no-no's\\\" as organizers try to keep fans and players safe.\"}, {\"start\": 314.64, \"end\": 323.68, \"text\": \"Masks are required and there will be no loud voices or jumping up and down in excitement.\"}, {\"start\": 323.68, \"end\": 332.36, \"text\": \"For social distancing only 5,000 people will be allowed in the stadium and they will have\"}, {\"start\": 332.36, \"end\": 341.08, \"text\": \"to fill out a form documenting their temperature for contact tracing in case there is an outbreak.\"}, {\"start\": 344.88, \"end\": 350.92, \"text\": \"The November presidential election is just four months away.\"}, {\"start\": 350.92, \"end\": 352.76, \"text\": \"And you know what that means?\"}, {\"start\": 352.76, \"end\": 361.84, \"text\": \"It means get ready for an onslaught of political as on television, in newspapers and on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 361.84, \"end\": 373.84, \"text\": \"In fact the campaign ads between President Trump and Joe Biden have already started heating up.\"}, {\"start\": 373.84, \"end\": 385.2, \"text\": \"The \\\"Campaign Media Analysis Group\\\" says of the more than 22,000 spots run by Trump since\"}, {\"start\": 385.2, \"end\": 394.759, \"text\": \"July 1, nearly all were negative, attacking Biden as soft on crime and unable to revive\"}, {\"start\": 394.76, \"end\": 399.2, \"text\": \"the struggling economy.\"}, {\"start\": 399.2, \"end\": 409.0, \"text\": \"In contrast \\\"Campaign Media Analysis Group\\\" says Biden has aired no negative ads but he\"}, {\"start\": 409.0, \"end\": 414.04, \"text\": \"frequently contrasts his record with Trump's.\"}, {\"start\": 414.04, \"end\": 425.16, \"text\": \"The latest Biden commercial is a warm salute to families, caring and commitment and suggests\"}, {\"start\": 425.22, \"end\": 430.72, \"text\": \"that Trump's negative ads are the kind of talk that hurts everyone, as the nation grapples\"}, {\"start\": 430.8, \"end\": 439.18, \"text\": \"with the pandemic, racial strife and economic hardship.\"}, {\"start\": 439.18, \"end\": 445.12, \"text\": \"Most of Trump's ads are airing in a broad range of states including some red ones where\"}, {\"start\": 445.12, \"end\": 451.18, \"text\": \"he clearly is trying to bolster his base.\"}, {\"start\": 451.18, \"end\": 459.1, \"text\": \"Biden's ads are airing in fewer places but many are playing in some critical swing states\"}, {\"start\": 459.1, \"end\": 464.48, \"text\": \"that Trump won in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 469.52, \"end\": 485.42, \"text\": \"Officials with Facebook and Instagram told CNN that its now banning all content that\"}, {\"start\": 485.42, \"end\": 488.14, \"text\": \"promotes conversion therapy.\"}, {\"start\": 488.14, \"end\": 494.28, \"text\": \"Conversion therapy refers to any attempt to change a person's sexual orientation or gender\"}, {\"start\": 494.34, \"end\": 501.04, \"text\": \"identity through seemingly scientific methods.\"}, {\"start\": 501.04, \"end\": 508.32, \"text\": \"It's been widely discredited and condemned by major medical associations.\"}, {\"start\": 508.32, \"end\": 517.86, \"text\": \"Studies show that people subjected to conversion therapy are put at a greater risk of depression\"}, {\"start\": 517.86, \"end\": 521.32, \"text\": \"or suicide.\"}, {\"start\": 521.32, \"end\": 527.88, \"text\": \"However it is still legal in many places in the world including the US and UK.\"}, {\"start\": 527.88, \"end\": 538.08, \"text\": \"Facebook says it will expand his existing policies on hate speech to include posts that\"}, {\"start\": 538.08, \"end\": 543.16, \"text\": \"advertise or promote conversion therapy.\"}, {\"start\": 543.16, \"end\": 554.1, \"text\": \"Facebook will also stop recommending content related to conversion therapy such as testimonials\"}, {\"start\": 554.1, \"end\": 561.58, \"text\": \"of its effectiveness or posts in praise or support of the practice, except those related\"}, {\"start\": 561.58, \"end\": 565.08, \"text\": \"to legislative content.\"}, {\"start\": 565.08, \"end\": 572.32, \"text\": \"Instagram banned conversion therapy ads earlier this year.\"}, {\"start\": 576.1, \"end\": 588.16, \"text\": \"On Friday President Trump commuted the sentence of his longtime friend and former campaign\"}, {\"start\": 588.2, \"end\": 590.54, \"text\": \"advisor Roger Stone.\"}, {\"start\": 590.56, \"end\": 597.92, \"text\": \"Stone was convicted in 2019 of seven charges of lying to Congress about his dealings with\"}, {\"start\": 597.92, \"end\": 609.14, \"text\": \"WikiLeaks and communications with Trump campaign officials during the probe into Russian interference\"}, {\"start\": 609.14, \"end\": 611.2, \"text\": \"in the 2016 election.\"}, {\"start\": 611.2, \"end\": 619.38, \"text\": \"Prosecutors say he lied to protect the president.\"}, {\"start\": 619.38, \"end\": 626.64, \"text\": \"Stone was set to report to a federal prison in Georgia in three days on July 14 to serve\"}, {\"start\": 626.64, \"end\": 629.3, \"text\": \"a 40 month sentence.\"}, {\"start\": 629.3, \"end\": 638.14, \"text\": \"But White House sources say Trump's commutation of Stone's sentence comes from the simple\"}, {\"start\": 638.14, \"end\": 649.36, \"text\": \"fact he has loathed the Russian investigation since the beginning and those close to Trump\"}, {\"start\": 649.36, \"end\": 658.24, \"text\": \"say he saw attacks on Stone as attacks against him.\"}, {\"start\": 658.28, \"end\": 665.02, \"text\": \"Now Stone says he wants to clear his name.\"}, {\"start\": 665.02, \"end\": 673.48, \"text\": \"During an interview with the press, Stone said \\\"I'd like to get a court room where we\"}, {\"start\": 673.48, \"end\": 681.06, \"text\": \"have a fair proceeding under honest judges and a system that is relatively fair.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 685.06, \"end\": 690.46, \"text\": \"Okay break out your pet photos.\"}, {\"start\": 690.5, \"end\": 694.4, \"text\": \"We know you've got 'em.\"}, {\"start\": 694.44, \"end\": 701.88, \"text\": \"They are probably taking up most of the space on your smart phone right now.\"}, {\"start\": 701.88, \"end\": 708.4, \"text\": \"Well Saturday is your day to share them.\"}, {\"start\": 708.44, \"end\": 714.02, \"text\": \"It's National All-American pet photo day!\"}, {\"start\": 714.02, \"end\": 725.9, \"text\": \"It's a day to celebrate those cute pet pics and share them for the world to see.\"}, {\"start\": 725.96, \"end\": 733.3, \"text\": \"These adorable dogs and cats that you're seeing now all belong to our Sign1News family.\"}, {\"start\": 733.3, \"end\": 744.5, \"text\": \"In fact you've probably already seen a few of them photo bombing a couple of our live\"}, {\"start\": 744.5, \"end\": 750.02, \"text\": \"broadcast while we're working from home.\"}, {\"start\": 750.02, \"end\": 756.58, \"text\": \"Hey my pets are here now.\"}, {\"start\": 756.58, \"end\": 760.0, \"text\": \"My dogs are coming now.\"}, {\"start\": 760.0, \"end\": 765.68, \"text\": \"This is Harley and this is Burton.\"}, {\"start\": 765.68, \"end\": 767.32, \"text\": \"Burton doesn't want to look into the camera.\"}, {\"start\": 767.32, \"end\": 771.3, \"text\": \"He prefers to look at me.\"}, {\"start\": 771.3, \"end\": 785.74, \"text\": \"You can show your pets on social media with the hashtag #allamericanpetphotoday.\"}, {\"start\": 789.12, \"end\": 791.34, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 791.34, \"end\": 792.94, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 792.94, \"end\": 796.02, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 796.02, \"end\": 806.9, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us in all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our app too.\"}, {\"start\": 806.9, \"end\": 812.12, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "U0RhuUss9YA": {
    "video_id": "U0RhuUss9YA",
    "title": "Google sued for alleged white men bias (ASL - 1.9.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180110",
    "duration": 73,
    "view_count": 127,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.8, \"end\": 11.16, \"text\": \"Two former Google software engineers are suing the company, alleging it discriminates against\"}, {\"start\": 11.16, \"end\": 17.619, \"text\": \"white people, conservatives and men.\"}, {\"start\": 17.62, \"end\": 21.8, \"text\": \"One of those suing Google is James Damore.\"}, {\"start\": 21.8, \"end\": 29.62, \"text\": \"He's the senior software engineer fired by Google last summer after a controversial essay\"}, {\"start\": 29.62, \"end\": 35.9, \"text\": \"he wrote about the company's diversity policies went viral.\"}, {\"start\": 35.96, \"end\": 45.0, \"text\": \"The lawsuit alleges Google awarded bonuses to employees who criticized Damore, kept internal\"}, {\"start\": 45.0, \"end\": 51.12, \"text\": \"blacklist to prevent conservative employees from getting opportunities at the company\"}, {\"start\": 51.12, \"end\": 57.86, \"text\": \"and failed to protect workers who supported President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 57.86, \"end\": 62.9, \"text\": \"The plaintiffs are seeking monetary and other damages.\"}, {\"start\": 63.02, \"end\": 71.48, \"text\": \"Google has said it has strong policies against workplace retaliation, harassment and discrimination.\"}]"
  },
  "EJZK1h7uh8g": {
    "video_id": "EJZK1h7uh8g",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.7.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180108",
    "duration": 465,
    "view_count": 948,
    "description": "1.7.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Terminal evacuated at JFK due to water main break\n-Bannon calls his \"Fire and Fury\" comments inaccurate\n-Boston firefighters battle fire and ice\n-Scorching heat wave in Australia\n-OJ Simpson threatens to sue Cosmopolitan Casino\n-Cleveland parade for winless Browns\n-One winner in $559M Powerball drawing\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, t",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.9, \"end\": 6.46, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.46, \"end\": 8.26, \"text\": \"Welcome the Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.26, \"end\": 9.38, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 9.38, \"end\": 11.94, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 13.3, \"end\": 24.02, \"text\": \"A water leak flooded a baggage claim area at JFK international Airport in New York today.\"}, {\"start\": 24.06, \"end\": 28.74, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 28.78, \"end\": 36.26, \"text\": \"The leak flooded the baggage holding area in Terminal 4.\"}, {\"start\": 36.26, \"end\": 46.74, \"text\": \"It caused flight delays and more headaches for the people who had already been delayed\"}, {\"start\": 46.74, \"end\": 53.06, \"text\": \"for hours because of the snow and ice.\"}, {\"start\": 53.06, \"end\": 62.26, \"text\": \"Hundreds of bags piled up because as new flights and new luggage came in there, there was no\"}, {\"start\": 62.38, \"end\": 67.18, \"text\": \"place to put them.\"}, {\"start\": 67.18, \"end\": 73.4, \"text\": \"Officials are telling people to come back later to retrieve their luggage.\"}, {\"start\": 73.4, \"end\": 80.58, \"text\": \"Some people are sleeping on the floor next to their suitcase hoping to get on a plane\"}, {\"start\": 80.58, \"end\": 82.84, \"text\": \"soon.\"}, {\"start\": 83.8, \"end\": 94.7, \"text\": \"President Trump's former top strategist Steve Bannon is calling his statements in the book\"}, {\"start\": 94.7, \"end\": 100.54, \"text\": \"\\\"Fire and Fury\\\" inaccurate.\"}, {\"start\": 100.54, \"end\": 107.74, \"text\": \"He says his support of the president and his agenda is unwavering.\"}, {\"start\": 107.74, \"end\": 116.6, \"text\": \"And he calls Donald Trump, Jr. a \\\"patriot\\\" and a \\\"good man.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 116.6, \"end\": 126.54, \"text\": \"But in the book Bannon calls Trump, Jr. \\\"treasonous\\\" and \\\"unpatriotic.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 126.54, \"end\": 131.72, \"text\": \"Bannon now says he regrets not issuing a statement about the book sooner.\"}, {\"start\": 131.72, \"end\": 140.76, \"text\": \"Earlier this week, after excerpts of the book were released, Trump tweeted that Bannon had\"}, {\"start\": 140.76, \"end\": 143.32, \"text\": \"\\\"lost his mind.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 144.16, \"end\": 153.3, \"text\": \"Boston firefighters had to battle extreme cold and icy conditions to put out a house\"}, {\"start\": 153.3, \"end\": 155.6, \"text\": \"fire Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 155.6, \"end\": 159.64, \"text\": \"Take a look at these pictures.\"}, {\"start\": 159.64, \"end\": 164.7, \"text\": \"It was so cold the water froze as it hit the house.\"}, {\"start\": 164.7, \"end\": 169.28, \"text\": \"The water also froze on the firefighter's helmets.\"}, {\"start\": 169.28, \"end\": 173.18, \"text\": \"None of the residents were hurt.\"}, {\"start\": 173.18, \"end\": 178.46, \"text\": \"One firefighter was treated for a non-life-threatening injury.\"}, {\"start\": 178.46, \"end\": 182.68, \"text\": \"The cause of the fire is under investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 183.68, \"end\": 193.82, \"text\": \"While the East coast of the United States is freezing right now, the East coast of Australia\"}, {\"start\": 193.82, \"end\": 199.58, \"text\": \"sizzled today with temperatures around 100 degrees.\"}, {\"start\": 199.58, \"end\": 212.52, \"text\": \"At 1 PM today Penrith in Sydney was the hottest place on earth at a scorching 117 degrees.\"}, {\"start\": 212.52, \"end\": 218.2, \"text\": \"Mission workers are patrolling the streets helping the homeless by handing out bottles\"}, {\"start\": 218.24, \"end\": 221.14, \"text\": \"of water.\"}, {\"start\": 221.14, \"end\": 229.24, \"text\": \"A massive wildfire broke out in Melbourne yesterday.\"}, {\"start\": 229.24, \"end\": 236.54, \"text\": \"It took 300 firefighters and three helicopters to contain it.\"}, {\"start\": 236.54, \"end\": 242.52, \"text\": \"It was later discovered the fire was deliberately set by 15-year-old girl.\"}, {\"start\": 243.3, \"end\": 256.5, \"text\": \"O.J. Simpson is threatening to sue the Cosmopolitan of Las Vegas over an incident at the strip\"}, {\"start\": 256.5, \"end\": 258.96, \"text\": \"resort last November.\"}, {\"start\": 258.96, \"end\": 269.96, \"text\": \"In a letter sent to media outlets Friday, Simpson's attorney said casino staff acted\"}, {\"start\": 269.96, \"end\": 277.14, \"text\": \"with malice and racial prejudice toward Simpson.\"}, {\"start\": 277.14, \"end\": 286.18, \"text\": \"Cosmo staffers are accused of falsely claiming Simpson was banned because he was drunk and\"}, {\"start\": 286.18, \"end\": 288.1, \"text\": \"disruptive.\"}, {\"start\": 288.1, \"end\": 295.36, \"text\": \"The incident allegedly happened shortly after Simpson was released from prison.\"}, {\"start\": 295.36, \"end\": 299.44, \"text\": \"Simpson it is now living in Las Vegas.\"}, {\"start\": 299.46, \"end\": 307.68, \"text\": \"The former NFL star is considering suing for at least $100 million.\"}, {\"start\": 307.68, \"end\": 314.28, \"text\": \"The Cosmopolitan of Las Vegas released a statement saying it does not comment on potential litigation.\"}, {\"start\": 315.4, \"end\": 326.72, \"text\": \"Thousands of Cleveland Brown fans took to the streets to mourn and protest the teams\"}, {\"start\": 326.72, \"end\": 330.06, \"text\": \"0-16 season.\"}, {\"start\": 330.06, \"end\": 338.74, \"text\": \"The Browns are just the second team in NFL history to go winless.\"}, {\"start\": 338.74, \"end\": 344.52, \"text\": \"Police estimated there were roughly 3,200 people there.\"}, {\"start\": 344.52, \"end\": 356.96, \"text\": \"Fans lined the streets around First Energy stadium to form a giant \\\"zero\\\".\"}, {\"start\": 356.98, \"end\": 369.62, \"text\": \"They brought in cars, buses, trucks, a rock band was brought in on a flatbed truck and\"}, {\"start\": 369.62, \"end\": 380.5, \"text\": \"one group carried 28 tombstones to represent the 28 quarterbacks the team has had since 1999.\"}, {\"start\": 380.54, \"end\": 388.7, \"text\": \"The Browns have won one game over the past two years combined and they haven't made the\"}, {\"start\": 388.72, \"end\": 392.4, \"text\": \"playoffs in 15 years.\"}, {\"start\": 393.58, \"end\": 399.02, \"text\": \"One lucky person in New Hampshire won Saturday's Powerball jackpot worth more than half a billion\"}, {\"start\": 399.02, \"end\": 401.54, \"text\": \"dollars!\"}, {\"start\": 401.54, \"end\": 415.42, \"text\": \"Only one ticket matched all six numbers for the estimated $559.7 million dollar prize.\"}, {\"start\": 415.48, \"end\": 422.92, \"text\": \"If the winner decides to take the lump cash sum, they'll take home about $352 million.\"}, {\"start\": 422.96, \"end\": 428.26, \"text\": \"There were several tickets that matched five numbers.\"}, {\"start\": 428.26, \"end\": 440.76, \"text\": \"Here are those winning numbers: 12, 29, 30, 33, 61 and Powerball 26.\"}, {\"start\": 441.86, \"end\": 443.8, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 443.8, \"end\": 445.08, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 445.08, \"end\": 447.16, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 447.16, \"end\": 450.92, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 450.92, \"end\": 456.8, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "pkfr-y5GRWo": {
    "video_id": "pkfr-y5GRWo",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.9.18",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180110",
    "duration": 598,
    "view_count": 802,
    "description": "1.9.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nToday's Headlines:\n-Trump meets with lawmakers to discuss DACA\n-Bannon stepping down from Breitbart\n-Google sued for alleged white men bias\n-California mudslides\n-Weight Watchers stock soars after Oprah speech\n-Same sex marriage now legal in Australia\n-NY commuters participate in \"No Pants Subway Ride\"\n-Alabama wins National Championship in overtime\n-Full video of deaf girl signing National Anthem\n\nSign1News i",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.68, \"end\": 7.04, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.04, \"end\": 9.12, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.14, \"end\": 10.7, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 10.7, \"end\": 13.44, \"text\": \"And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.96, \"end\": 23.82, \"text\": \"President Trump sat down today with lawmakers to discuss several major issues facing Congress\"}, {\"start\": 23.82, \"end\": 37.3, \"text\": \"right now: Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals (DACA), the border wall and so-called chain\"}, {\"start\": 37.3, \"end\": 41.08, \"text\": \"immigration.\"}, {\"start\": 41.08, \"end\": 45.46, \"text\": \"Republicans and Democrats are coming together to discuss these issues.\"}, {\"start\": 45.46, \"end\": 51.7, \"text\": \"Both sides came to a rare agreement that finding a solution is going to take both parties cooperating.\"}, {\"start\": 51.7, \"end\": 57.52, \"text\": \"Meanwhile the government is scheduled to run out of money in just 10 days on January 19th.\"}, {\"start\": 57.52, \"end\": 63.86, \"text\": \"Congress is scrambling to come to an agreement on how to fund the government.\"}, {\"start\": 63.92, \"end\": 68.12, \"text\": \"The Republican plan will need Democratic support to pass.\"}, {\"start\": 68.12, \"end\": 75.1, \"text\": \"And Democrats say any funding plan will have to include a solution to DACA.\"}, {\"start\": 77.48, \"end\": 86.6, \"text\": \"President Trump's former chief strategist Steve Bannon has stepped down has as Executive\"}, {\"start\": 86.62, \"end\": 94.2, \"text\": \"Chairman of the Breitbart News Network.\"}, {\"start\": 94.2, \"end\": 96.36, \"text\": \"Employees say they were stunned by the decision.\"}, {\"start\": 96.36, \"end\": 101.38, \"text\": \"Bannon ran the news website from 2012 to 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 101.38, \"end\": 108.72, \"text\": \"In 2016 Trump hired him to run his presidential campaign.\"}, {\"start\": 108.72, \"end\": 114.64, \"text\": \"But in 2017 Bannon was fired by Trump and he returned Breitbart.\"}, {\"start\": 114.64, \"end\": 116.8, \"text\": \"Now he's out at Breitbart again.\"}, {\"start\": 116.8, \"end\": 126.38, \"text\": \"If you recall Bannon angered President Trump last week when it was revealed he called the\"}, {\"start\": 126.38, \"end\": 133.72, \"text\": \"2016 Trump Tower meeting with a Russian lawyer \\\"treasonous\\\" in the new book \\\"Fire and Fury.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 133.72, \"end\": 140.9, \"text\": \"Sources told CNN that after those comments, there was a hard push at Breitbart to convince\"}, {\"start\": 140.92, \"end\": 143.12, \"text\": \"the CEO to fire him.\"}, {\"start\": 145.52, \"end\": 156.26, \"text\": \"Two former Google software engineers are suing the company, alleging it discriminates against\"}, {\"start\": 156.26, \"end\": 162.6, \"text\": \"white people, conservatives and men.\"}, {\"start\": 162.6, \"end\": 166.8, \"text\": \"One of those suing Google is James Damore.\"}, {\"start\": 166.8, \"end\": 173.72, \"text\": \"He's the senior software engineer fired by Google last summer after a controversial essay\"}, {\"start\": 173.72, \"end\": 181.04, \"text\": \"he wrote about the company's diversity policies went viral.\"}, {\"start\": 181.04, \"end\": 190.82, \"text\": \"The lawsuit alleges Google awarded bonuses to employees who criticized Damore, kept internal\"}, {\"start\": 190.82, \"end\": 196.06, \"text\": \"blacklist to prevent conservative employees from getting opportunities at the company\"}, {\"start\": 196.06, \"end\": 202.6, \"text\": \"and failed to protect workers who supported President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 202.6, \"end\": 207.58, \"text\": \"The plaintiffs are seeking monetary and other damages.\"}, {\"start\": 207.58, \"end\": 216.76, \"text\": \"Google has said it has strong policies against workplace retaliation, harassment and discrimination.\"}, {\"start\": 219.54, \"end\": 231.06, \"text\": \"Storms in Southern California brought heavy rains and triggered mudslides that killed\"}, {\"start\": 231.06, \"end\": 233.86, \"text\": \"eight people.\"}, {\"start\": 233.86, \"end\": 238.88, \"text\": \"Firefighters spent Tuesday rescuing survivors trapped in the mud.\"}, {\"start\": 238.88, \"end\": 249.34, \"text\": \"Torrential rains overnight and into Tuesday totaled more than 4 inches in areas already\"}, {\"start\": 249.34, \"end\": 251.24, \"text\": \"scarred by wildfires.\"}, {\"start\": 251.24, \"end\": 258.98, \"text\": \"Some communities saw rain fall at more than one and a half inches per hour.\"}, {\"start\": 259.02, \"end\": 269.02, \"text\": \"More than 6,000 residents in Santa Barbara County are under mandatory evacuation orders\"}, {\"start\": 269.02, \"end\": 271.48, \"text\": \"due to the storm.\"}, {\"start\": 274.1, \"end\": 287.96, \"text\": \"Right after Oprah Winfrey's Golden Globes speech Sunday night, Weight Watchers shares\"}, {\"start\": 287.96, \"end\": 289.96, \"text\": \"jumped 13-percent.\"}, {\"start\": 289.96, \"end\": 296.86, \"text\": \"It was because of the speculation Winfrey might run for president.\"}, {\"start\": 296.86, \"end\": 304.36, \"text\": \"Winfrey is an owner of the weight loss company.\"}, {\"start\": 304.36, \"end\": 311.72, \"text\": \"Winfrey has publicly backed Weight Watchers for years, attributing her weight loss success\"}, {\"start\": 311.72, \"end\": 313.94, \"text\": \"to its diet regimen.\"}, {\"start\": 313.94, \"end\": 322.4, \"text\": \"Winfrey bought a 10-percent stake in the struggling company in October 2015 and joined its Board\"}, {\"start\": 322.4, \"end\": 324.24, \"text\": \"of Directors.\"}, {\"start\": 324.24, \"end\": 330.64, \"text\": \"Since then Weight Watchers enrollment has climbed by nearly 1 million members.\"}, {\"start\": 333.0, \"end\": 339.66, \"text\": \"Today marks the first day that same-sex couples could be legally married in Australia.\"}, {\"start\": 339.66, \"end\": 351.2, \"text\": \"Some couples lined up at midnight at Australia's Parliament House.\"}, {\"start\": 351.2, \"end\": 358.5, \"text\": \"When the clock struck 12:01 AM they wanted to be the first same-sex couple in Australia's\"}, {\"start\": 358.5, \"end\": 360.72, \"text\": \"history to tie the knot.\"}, {\"start\": 360.72, \"end\": 365.24, \"text\": \"Same-sex marriage legislation was passed last December which made the unions legal.\"}, {\"start\": 367.3, \"end\": 373.5, \"text\": \"This weekend several New Yorkers braved the frigid winter temperatures to participate\"}, {\"start\": 373.5, \"end\": 381.32, \"text\": \"in the 17th annual \\\"No Pants Subway Ride.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 381.32, \"end\": 391.96, \"text\": \"Riders board subway cars at random without their pants and keep a straight face -- as\"}, {\"start\": 391.96, \"end\": 394.88, \"text\": \"if nothing is wrong.\"}, {\"start\": 394.88, \"end\": 404.14, \"text\": \"The event was started in 2002 by comedy group \\\"Improv Everywhere\\\"and it has now spread\"}, {\"start\": 404.18, \"end\": 407.7, \"text\": \"to 60 cities around the world.\"}, {\"start\": 409.8, \"end\": 418.2, \"text\": \"Congratulations to head coach Nick Saban and the Alabama Crimson Tide.\"}, {\"start\": 418.2, \"end\": 429.04, \"text\": \"Last night in Atlanta, Alabama pulled off an epic come back to beat Georgia 26-23 in\"}, {\"start\": 429.04, \"end\": 431.34, \"text\": \"overtime to win the college football national championship.\"}, {\"start\": 431.34, \"end\": 441.16, \"text\": \"With the win Saban ties legendary Alabama coach Bear Bryant with a record six national\"}, {\"start\": 441.16, \"end\": 442.86, \"text\": \"championships.\"}, {\"start\": 445.48, \"end\": 451.82, \"text\": \"We know many of you tuned into the national championship game just to see 12-year-old\"}, {\"start\": 451.82, \"end\": 456.86, \"text\": \"Carly Ortega sign the national anthem.\"}, {\"start\": 456.86, \"end\": 461.46, \"text\": \"Unfortunately the ESPN cameras did not spotlight her.\"}, {\"start\": 461.46, \"end\": 462.92, \"text\": \"But don't worry.\"}, {\"start\": 462.92, \"end\": 471.5, \"text\": \"Thanks to the staff at Atlanta Area School for the Deaf, we have the full video of her amazing\"}, {\"start\": 471.5, \"end\": 472.52, \"text\": \"performance.\"}, {\"start\": 472.52, \"end\": 474.04, \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"}, {\"start\": 572.76, \"end\": 575.2, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 575.2, \"end\": 576.56, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 576.56, \"end\": 579.04, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 579.04, \"end\": 584.16, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 584.16, \"end\": 591.8, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "rErFQSndqkE": {
    "video_id": "rErFQSndqkE",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.9.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180410",
    "duration": 556,
    "view_count": 1902,
    "description": "4.9.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Topless protestor at Cosby retrial \n-Explosives set off in Sam’s Club\n-More National Guard Troops arrive at border\n-Zuckerberg set to be grilled by Congress on Tuesday\n-Co-founder of Apple leaving Facebook\n-Group claims YouTube collects data from kids\n-Spring flowers bloom on Prince memorial\n-National Pet Day pictures reminder\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 9.52, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.52, \"end\": 11.66, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.66, \"end\": 13.26, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 13.26, \"end\": 16.04, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.66, \"end\": 30.66, \"text\": \"Opening statements in Bill Cosby's sex assault retrial began today in Pennsylvania.\"}, {\"start\": 30.92, \"end\": 38.1, \"text\": \"The case will hang on the word of Andrea Constand.\"}, {\"start\": 38.1, \"end\": 45.14, \"text\": \"Constand says she was at Cosby's home near Philadelphia in January 2004 when she says\"}, {\"start\": 45.14, \"end\": 48.7, \"text\": \"he drugged her then assaulted her.\"}, {\"start\": 48.7, \"end\": 55.22, \"text\": \"In Cosby's first trial, his attorneys argued he and Constand had a consensual sexual relationship\"}, {\"start\": 55.22, \"end\": 59.32, \"text\": \"and they questioned her version of what happened.\"}, {\"start\": 59.32, \"end\": 65.3, \"text\": \"That trial ended in a hung jury.\"}, {\"start\": 65.44, \"end\": 72.36, \"text\": \"But something strange happened today as Cosby was walking into the courthouse.\"}, {\"start\": 72.36, \"end\": 77.82, \"text\": \"A half naked woman jumped in front of him.\"}, {\"start\": 88.98, \"end\": 93.08, \"text\": \"The woman was a protester chanting \\\"Women's lives matter!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 93.08, \"end\": 96.24, \"text\": \"As you saw, she was quickly taken down by police.\"}, {\"start\": 96.24, \"end\": 103.16, \"text\": \"Police later identified her as Nicolle Rochelle from New Jersey.\"}, {\"start\": 103.16, \"end\": 112.06, \"text\": \"And according to her IMDb page, she appeared on four episodes of \\\"The Cosby Show\\\" between\"}, {\"start\": 112.14, \"end\": 114.82, \"text\": \"1990 and 1992.\"}, {\"start\": 118.44, \"end\": 129.04, \"text\": \"Police in Ontario, California still don't know why 49-year-old Hugo Gonzales\"}, {\"start\": 129.04, \"end\": 137.82, \"text\": \"detonated two explosives inside a Southern California Sam's Club last week.\"}, {\"start\": 137.82, \"end\": 142.54, \"text\": \"They released this surveillance video of Gonzales walking into the store.\"}, {\"start\": 142.54, \"end\": 147.5, \"text\": \"He was wearing a medical mask and an LA Dodgers hat.\"}, {\"start\": 147.5, \"end\": 155.72, \"text\": \"If you look at the video closely, you will see a quick flash and employees and shoppers reaction.\"}, {\"start\": 172.46, \"end\": 175.76, \"text\": \"No one was injured and there was no significant damage.\"}, {\"start\": 175.76, \"end\": 179.84, \"text\": \"Employees used fire extinguishers to put out the flames.\"}, {\"start\": 179.84, \"end\": 185.44, \"text\": \"Gonzales was arrested 3 miles from the Sam's Club after a short pursuit.\"}, {\"start\": 185.44, \"end\": 198.52, \"text\": \"He is charged with suspicion of arson and possession of a destructive device.\"}, {\"start\": 198.52, \"end\": 204.36, \"text\": \"Police are still investigating a motive.\"}, {\"start\": 204.36, \"end\": 210.2, \"text\": \"They say Gonzales is not connected with any known criminal organizations, he is not on\"}, {\"start\": 210.2, \"end\": 218.86, \"text\": \"a terrorist watch list nor has he ever worked at Sam's Club.\"}, {\"start\": 223.68, \"end\": 232.16, \"text\": \"Today more National Guard troops are headed to the US-Mexico border.\"}, {\"start\": 232.28, \"end\": 236.7, \"text\": \"And thousands are still on the way.\"}, {\"start\": 236.7, \"end\": 248.08, \"text\": \"The troops are joining agents patrolling the border on the ground, in the air and on water.\"}, {\"start\": 248.08, \"end\": 254.6, \"text\": \"Today in Texas alone, 250 members will be sent to the US-Mexico border.\"}, {\"start\": 254.6, \"end\": 262.78, \"text\": \"President Trump ordered the military to secure the border until his border wall is built.\"}, {\"start\": 262.78, \"end\": 270.18, \"text\": \"US troops will not be able to enforce immigration laws however.\"}, {\"start\": 270.18, \"end\": 275.4, \"text\": \"Instead, the guard will serve in support roles like training and construction.\"}, {\"start\": 278.64, \"end\": 285.94, \"text\": \"Facebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg is in Washington DC.\"}, {\"start\": 286.02, \"end\": 293.04, \"text\": \"He is set to be questioned about the data controversy in front of Congress Tuesday and\"}, {\"start\": 293.04, \"end\": 294.74, \"text\": \"Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 294.74, \"end\": 301.38, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg's widely anticipated testimony comes after Facebook revealed Cambridge Analytica\"}, {\"start\": 301.48, \"end\": 310.32, \"text\": \"may have had data on 87 million of its users.\"}, {\"start\": 310.32, \"end\": 318.6, \"text\": \"Also today Facebook will start alerting users whose data was harvested by Cambridge Analytica.\"}, {\"start\": 318.6, \"end\": 326.17, \"text\": \"The link will be posted on your Facebook news feed and will show what apps are linked to\"}, {\"start\": 326.17, \"end\": 328.36, \"text\": \"your accounts.\"}, {\"start\": 328.36, \"end\": 334.82, \"text\": \"Facebook said users would have the opportunity to use the link to delete apps and prevent\"}, {\"start\": 334.92, \"end\": 338.38, \"text\": \"them from collecting more information.\"}, {\"start\": 340.54, \"end\": 350.84, \"text\": \"Apple co-founder Steve Wozniak says he is leaving Facebook over its recent data controversy.\"}, {\"start\": 350.84, \"end\": 361.04, \"text\": \"In an email to USA Today, Wosniak said: \\\"Users provide every detail of their lives to Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 361.04, \"end\": 365.52, \"text\": \"and Facebook makes a lot of advertising money off of this.\"}, {\"start\": 365.64, \"end\": 371.26, \"text\": \"But users get none of the profits back.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 371.26, \"end\": 380.52, \"text\": \"Wozniak said he'd rather pay for Facebook than have his personal information exploited\"}, {\"start\": 380.52, \"end\": 383.96, \"text\": \"for advertising.\"}, {\"start\": 388.44, \"end\": 400.44, \"text\": \"Twenty advocacy groups filed a complaint against YouTube today claiming it allegedly profits\"}, {\"start\": 400.44, \"end\": 402.78, \"text\": \"off young viewers.\"}, {\"start\": 402.78, \"end\": 414.52, \"text\": \"The groups consist of child, consumer and privacy coalitions.\"}, {\"start\": 414.52, \"end\": 423.28, \"text\": \"They claim YouTube illegally collected data on 23 million children over an undisclosed amount\"}, {\"start\": 423.36, \"end\": 431.04, \"text\": \"of time, violating the Child Online Privacy Protection Act.\"}, {\"start\": 431.04, \"end\": 438.88, \"text\": \"The groups are asking the Federal Trade Commission (FTC) to investigate and, if found guilty,\"}, {\"start\": 438.88, \"end\": 445.44, \"text\": \"fine YouTube up to roughly $41,000 per violation.\"}, {\"start\": 445.44, \"end\": 452.08, \"text\": \"YouTube's terms of service say it is not for anyone under 13 but it still easy for young\"}, {\"start\": 452.08, \"end\": 455.44, \"text\": \"child to sign up for an account.\"}, {\"start\": 457.84, \"end\": 471.92, \"text\": \"Two years ago California artist Christine Stein created this mural to honor music icon Prince.\"}, {\"start\": 471.92, \"end\": 474.64, \"text\": \"It's sits right in front of her yard.\"}, {\"start\": 474.64, \"end\": 481.92, \"text\": \"But this year, a spring surprise added a lovely touch to the mural.\"}, {\"start\": 481.92, \"end\": 487.68, \"text\": \"The mural has grown a new crop of flowers and it looks just like hair.\"}, {\"start\": 487.68, \"end\": 494.4, \"text\": \"Stein was stunned because she didn't even know the tree behind the mural had flowers.\"}, {\"start\": 494.4, \"end\": 498.32, \"text\": \"Images of the mural have quickly spread on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 500.96, \"end\": 505.2, \"text\": \"Thank you to everyone that sent us pictures of your pets.\"}, {\"start\": 505.2, \"end\": 507.4, \"text\": \"They are adorable!\"}, {\"start\": 507.4, \"end\": 512.8, \"text\": \"If you haven't sent your pictures, you still have time.\"}, {\"start\": 512.82, \"end\": 517.6, \"text\": \"National Pet Day is this Wednesday, April 11.\"}, {\"start\": 517.6, \"end\": 524.0, \"text\": \"Send your pictures to our Sign1News Facebook page and we will share them with our viewers\"}, {\"start\": 524.0, \"end\": 526.64, \"text\": \"during our broadcast.\"}, {\"start\": 526.8, \"end\": 530.22, \"text\": \"So keep them coming!\"}, {\"start\": 532.68, \"end\": 535.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 535.0, \"end\": 536.42, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 536.42, \"end\": 538.7, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 538.7, \"end\": 542.8, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 542.8, \"end\": 544.08, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 544.08, \"end\": 545.42, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 545.42, \"end\": 548.56, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "v7Gio5YC4YY": {
    "video_id": "v7Gio5YC4YY",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.11.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171012",
    "duration": 546,
    "view_count": 163,
    "description": "News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).\n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n\n-CALIFORNIA NEIGHBORHOODS IN RUINS\n-OFFICER DRIVES THROUGH WILDFIRES\n-WEINSTEIN'S WIFE IS LEAVING HIM\n-TERRY CREWS SHARES SEXUAL ASSAULT STORY\n-NY MAN ARRESTED FOR USING LAS VEGAS IN THREAT\n-ZUCKERBERG APOLOGIZES TO PUERTO RICO\n-WHAT TO KNOW ABOUT EQUIFAX HACK\n-TATTOOS THAT TRACK YOUR HEALTH\n-DOGS SNUGGLE TO THE RESCUE IN LAS VEGAS\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to d",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am\"}, {\"start\": 13.0, \"end\": 17.0, \"text\": \"Candace Jones. And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.0, \"end\": 25.0, \"text\": \"In California wildfires continue to destroy\"}, {\"start\": 25.0, \"end\": 30.0, \"text\": \"acre after acre. At least 17 people have been killed\"}, {\"start\": 31.0, \"end\": 35.0, \"text\": \"and more than 20,000 have been evacuated.\"}, {\"start\": 35.0, \"end\": 40.0, \"text\": \"Fire officials say about 2,000 homes\"}, {\"start\": 40.0, \"end\": 45.0, \"text\": \"and businesses have been destroyed. Strong winds\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 50.0, \"text\": \"and low humidity are\"}, {\"start\": 51.0, \"end\": 55.0, \"text\": \"fueling the wildfires.\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 60.0, \"text\": \"Some people have been able to return to their\"}, {\"start\": 62.0, \"end\": 67.0, \"text\": \"homes to try and pick up the pieces.\"}, {\"start\": 68.0, \"end\": 73.0, \"text\": \"In other areas, wildfires are still forcing people\"}, {\"start\": 73.0, \"end\": 78.0, \"text\": \"out of their homes. Unfortunately, for\"}, {\"start\": 78.0, \"end\": 82.0, \"text\": \"the next seven days there is no\"}, {\"start\": 82.0, \"end\": 87.0, \"text\": \"rain in the forecast.\"}, {\"start\": 89.0, \"end\": 94.0, \"text\": \"Officials believe this will be the worst\"}, {\"start\": 94.0, \"end\": 100.0, \"text\": \"disaster in California history and\"}, {\"start\": 100.0, \"end\": 105.0, \"text\": \"they're just trying to keep people safe.\"}, {\"start\": 108.0, \"end\": 113.0, \"text\": \"This is amazing video.\"}, {\"start\": 113.0, \"end\": 117.0, \"text\": \"Sunday night a brave Sonoma County\"}, {\"start\": 117.0, \"end\": 122.0, \"text\": \"sheriff's deputy\"}, {\"start\": 122.0, \"end\": 129.0, \"text\": \"shot this video while driving through the wildfires.\"}, {\"start\": 129.0, \"end\": 131.0, \"text\": \"The video takes us\"}, {\"start\": 133.0, \"end\": 137.0, \"text\": \"inside the blaze as it destroys\"}, {\"start\": 137.0, \"end\": 144.0, \"text\": \"everything in its path.\"}, {\"start\": 144.0, \"end\": 148.0, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 148.0, \"end\": 153.0, \"text\": \"The sheriff's office posted the video on their Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 153.0, \"end\": 158.0, \"text\": \"page. At the end of the post\"}, {\"start\": 158.0, \"end\": 162.0, \"text\": \"the sheriff wrote \\\"Please be safe, be\"}, {\"start\": 162.0, \"end\": 168.0, \"text\": \"calm and be caring of your neighbors.\"}, {\"start\": 168.0, \"end\": 172.0, \"text\": \"We will get through this\"}, {\"start\": 172.0, \"end\": 176.0, \"text\": \"disaster together.\"}, {\"start\": 179.0, \"end\": 184.0, \"text\": \"Georgina Chapman, wife\"}, {\"start\": 185.0, \"end\": 189.0, \"text\": \"of Hollywood producer Harvey\"}, {\"start\": 190.0, \"end\": 195.0, \"text\": \"Weinstein, says she is leaving her\"}, {\"start\": 195.0, \"end\": 200.0, \"text\": \"husband. They have been married for 10 years and have two\"}, {\"start\": 200.0, \"end\": 201.0, \"text\": \"children together.\"}, {\"start\": 201.0, \"end\": 206.0, \"text\": \"Her announcement comes after dozens of women\"}, {\"start\": 208.0, \"end\": 212.0, \"text\": \"have accused her husband of rape,\"}, {\"start\": 212.0, \"end\": 218.0, \"text\": \"abuse and other forms of sexual harassment.\"}, {\"start\": 219.0, \"end\": 224.0, \"text\": \"Chapman says her heart\"}, {\"start\": 224.0, \"end\": 229.0, \"text\": \"breaks for all of the women who have suffered pain\"}, {\"start\": 229.0, \"end\": 234.0, \"text\": \"because of her husband's\"}, {\"start\": 234.0, \"end\": 237.0, \"text\": \"unforgivable actions.\"}, {\"start\": 239.0, \"end\": 244.0, \"text\": \"Former NFL star and actor\"}, {\"start\": 244.0, \"end\": 249.0, \"text\": \"Terry Crews says that he was\"}, {\"start\": 249.0, \"end\": 257.0, \"text\": \"sexually assaulted by a Hollywood executive.\"}, {\"start\": 257.0, \"end\": 262.0, \"text\": \"Tuesday he tweeted a male film executive,\"}, {\"start\": 263.0, \"end\": 268.0, \"text\": \"who he didn't name, groped him at\"}, {\"start\": 268.0, \"end\": 271.0, \"text\": \"a Hollywood event\"}, {\"start\": 273.0, \"end\": 277.0, \"text\": \"last year.\"}, {\"start\": 277.0, \"end\": 281.0, \"text\": \"Crews said if he\"}, {\"start\": 282.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"reported the incident he was afraid he would lose his job.\"}, {\"start\": 287.0, \"end\": 288.0, \"text\": \"So he let it go.\"}, {\"start\": 288.0, \"end\": 292.0, \"text\": \"Crews also said that Harvey\"}, {\"start\": 294.0, \"end\": 298.0, \"text\": \"Weinstein is not the only perpetrator\"}, {\"start\": 300.0, \"end\": 303.0, \"text\": \"and he wants other\"}, {\"start\": 305.0, \"end\": 308.0, \"text\": \"sexual assault victims to know\"}, {\"start\": 310.0, \"end\": 313.0, \"text\": \"that they are not alone.\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 321.0, \"text\": \"Facebook CEO Mark\"}, {\"start\": 322.0, \"end\": 327.0, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg is apologizing for the way he announced Facebook would join\"}, {\"start\": 328.0, \"end\": 333.0, \"text\": \"in the relief efforts for Puerto Rico. He used the virtual\"}, {\"start\": 333.0, \"end\": 338.0, \"text\": \"reality app called \\\"Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 343.0, \"text\": \"Spaces\\\" to create this video.\"}, {\"start\": 343.0, \"end\": 348.0, \"text\": \"In that video Zuckerberg is\"}, {\"start\": 349.0, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"a cartoon avatar that has\"}, {\"start\": 354.0, \"end\": 359.0, \"text\": \"teleported to Puerto Rico. Some of the damage to the\"}, {\"start\": 359.0, \"end\": 364.0, \"text\": \"island can be seen during the animated character's tour.\"}, {\"start\": 364.0, \"end\": 368.0, \"text\": \"Some have criticized\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 374.0, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg for being insensitive and they\"}, {\"start\": 374.0, \"end\": 380.0, \"text\": \"accuse him of taking advantage of the disaster.\"}, {\"start\": 380.0, \"end\": 385.0, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg said he wanted to\"}, {\"start\": 385.0, \"end\": 390.0, \"text\": \"show how virtual reality can raise awareness\"}, {\"start\": 390.0, \"end\": 395.0, \"text\": \"and share news of Facebook's partnership\"}, {\"start\": 398.0, \"end\": 402.0, \"text\": \"with the Red Cross. He expressed regret\"}, {\"start\": 403.0, \"end\": 407.0, \"text\": \"saying quote \\\"Reading some of the comments,\"}, {\"start\": 407.0, \"end\": 411.0, \"text\": \"I realize my intention wasn't clear\"}, {\"start\": 412.0, \"end\": 415.0, \"text\": \"and I'm sorry to anyone this offended.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 417.0, \"end\": 422.0, \"text\": \"Your next tattoo might be able to\"}, {\"start\": 422.0, \"end\": 427.0, \"text\": \"help you track your health.\"}, {\"start\": 428.0, \"end\": 432.0, \"text\": \"Researchers at Harvard Medical School and MIT\"}, {\"start\": 434.0, \"end\": 439.0, \"text\": \"have designed new tattoo ink\"}, {\"start\": 439.0, \"end\": 443.0, \"text\": \"that changes color according\"}, {\"start\": 443.0, \"end\": 448.0, \"text\": \"to your body chemistry. For example, if your\"}, {\"start\": 448.0, \"end\": 453.0, \"text\": \"glucose levels increase, the green in your tattoo\"}, {\"start\": 454.0, \"end\": 460.0, \"text\": \"will darken to brown.\"}, {\"start\": 461.0, \"end\": 462.0, \"text\": \"Researchers are hoping\"}, {\"start\": 463.124, \"end\": 468.124, \"text\": \"the innovation will help people better monitor their health.\"}, {\"start\": 471.0, \"end\": 476.0, \"text\": \"After the shooting in Las Vegas many were left\"}, {\"start\": 477.0, \"end\": 479.0, \"text\": \"with emotional scars.\"}, {\"start\": 479.0, \"end\": 484.0, \"text\": \"That's where a dog named \\\"Willow\\\" comes in. She is a\"}, {\"start\": 484.0, \"end\": 489.0, \"text\": \"service dog. Willow and other dogs from around the country\"}, {\"start\": 489.0, \"end\": 494.0, \"text\": \"are being brought to Las Vegas to give love, affection\"}, {\"start\": 494.0, \"end\": 499.0, \"text\": \"and attention to the people who need it.\"}, {\"start\": 500.0, \"end\": 506.0, \"text\": \"The dogs lay or sit next to people so they can pet or hug them.\"}, {\"start\": 506.0, \"end\": 510.0, \"text\": \"Their number one goal is to put a smile on people's faces.\"}, {\"start\": 514.0, \"end\": 517.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories. I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 517.0, \"end\": 521.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Remember\"}, {\"start\": 521.0, \"end\": 526.0, \"text\": \"to \\\"Like\\\" us on Facebook and\"}, {\"start\": 527.0, \"end\": 530.0, \"text\": \"follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 530.024, \"end\": 537.024, \"text\": \"Sign1 News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "HCkAYRQSKTc": {
    "video_id": "HCkAYRQSKTc",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.3.17- News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171104",
    "duration": 567,
    "view_count": 152,
    "description": "November 3, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-TRUMP HEADS TO ASIA FOR 12-DAY TRIP\n-BERGDAHL DISHONORABLE DISCHARGE, NO JAIL TIME\n-WALMART SHOOTING SUSPECT APPEARS IN COURT\n-REMEMBERING THE NYC BIKE PATH VICTIMS\n-AMERICANS MORE STRESSED THAN EVER  \n-LONG LINES OUTSIDE APPLE STORES  \n-ASTROS ARRIVE BACK IN HOUSTON\n-TIME CHANGE AND BODY CLOCK\n\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality n",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 11.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 11.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.0, \"end\": 22.0, \"text\": \"President Trump begins a 12 day trip to Asia starting today.\"}, {\"start\": 23.0, \"end\": 28.0, \"text\": \"White House officials say the trip has two main\"}, {\"start\": 28.0, \"end\": 33.0, \"text\": \"objectives: the rising nuclear threat of North\"}, {\"start\": 33.0, \"end\": 38.0, \"text\": \"Korea and trade. North Korea\"}, {\"start\": 38.0, \"end\": 43.0, \"text\": \"is a top priority. Trump is considering\"}, {\"start\": 44.0, \"end\": 48.0, \"text\": \"putting North Korea back on the list of state\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"sponsors of terrorism.\"}, {\"start\": 53.0, \"end\": 58.0, \"text\": \"He wants to convince other countries in the region\"}, {\"start\": 58.0, \"end\": 63.0, \"text\": \"North Korea threatens, not just our allies,\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 68.0, \"text\": \"but is a threat to the entire world.\"}, {\"start\": 72.0, \"end\": 76.0, \"text\": \"Last month U.S. Army Sergeant Bowe\"}, {\"start\": 76.0, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"Bergdahl pleaded guilty to desertion\"}, {\"start\": 81.0, \"end\": 85.0, \"text\": \"and misbehavior before the enemy.\"}, {\"start\": 85.0, \"end\": 90.0, \"text\": \"He is the soldier held captive by\"}, {\"start\": 91.0, \"end\": 95.0, \"text\": \"Afghanistan Taliban for\"}, {\"start\": 95.0, \"end\": 100.0, \"text\": \"five years after deserting his post.\"}, {\"start\": 101.0, \"end\": 105.0, \"text\": \"Then he was released in a controversial prison exchange.\"}, {\"start\": 106.0, \"end\": 111.0, \"text\": \"Today a military judge sentenced Bergdahl.\"}, {\"start\": 112.0, \"end\": 118.0, \"text\": \"He received a dishonorable discharge\"}, {\"start\": 118.0, \"end\": 122.0, \"text\": \"but avoided jail time.\"}, {\"start\": 122.0, \"end\": 127.0, \"text\": \"His rank was dropped from sergeant\"}, {\"start\": 127.0, \"end\": 132.0, \"text\": \"to private\"}, {\"start\": 133.0, \"end\": 138.0, \"text\": \"and he has to pay a fine of ten thousand dollars\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 142.0, \"text\": \"over the next 10 months.\"}, {\"start\": 142.0, \"end\": 148.0, \"text\": \"Bergdahl cried during the sentencing.\"}, {\"start\": 148.0, \"end\": 153.0, \"text\": \"He apologized and asked for forgiveness from the soldiers who were\"}, {\"start\": 153.0, \"end\": 157.0, \"text\": \"injured trying to rescue him.\"}, {\"start\": 160.0, \"end\": 164.0, \"text\": \"Scott Ostrem made his first court appearance\"}, {\"start\": 164.0, \"end\": 169.0, \"text\": \"today. He is the man suspected of killing three\"}, {\"start\": 169.0, \"end\": 174.0, \"text\": \"people in a Colorado Wal-Mart.\"}, {\"start\": 174.0, \"end\": 178.0, \"text\": \"Witnesses say he casually strolled into the\"}, {\"start\": 178.0, \"end\": 185.0, \"text\": \"store Wednesday night, opened fire near a cash register\"}, {\"start\": 185.0, \"end\": 191.0, \"text\": \"and calmly walked back out.\"}, {\"start\": 191.0, \"end\": 194.0, \"text\": \"Police captured him the next day.\"}, {\"start\": 194.0, \"end\": 201.0, \"text\": \"Investigators say they don't know why Ostrem did it.\"}, {\"start\": 202.0, \"end\": 209.0, \"text\": \"Right now they believe it was a random act of violence.\"}, {\"start\": 213.0, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"New York authorities are putting hundreds of concrete\"}, {\"start\": 217.0, \"end\": 225.0, \"text\": \"barriers in place along the Hudson River Park bike path.\"}, {\"start\": 225.0, \"end\": 231.0, \"text\": \"They are intended to keep vehicles from accessing the path.\"}, {\"start\": 231.0, \"end\": 235.0, \"text\": \"On Tuesday a man drove a rented truck down part of the\"}, {\"start\": 235.0, \"end\": 241.0, \"text\": \"path killing eight people and injuring several others.\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 245.0, \"text\": \"Memorials have also sprung up at spots. Some are right\"}, {\"start\": 245.0, \"end\": 250.0, \"text\": \"next to the newly installed barriers. Thursday night there was a\"}, {\"start\": 250.0, \"end\": 254.0, \"text\": \"candlelight vigil for the bike path victims.\"}, {\"start\": 256.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"Dozens of people showed up to remember them.\"}, {\"start\": 262.0, \"end\": 266.0, \"text\": \"And in Washington D.C. there was a moment of silence\"}, {\"start\": 266.0, \"end\": 271.0, \"text\": \"on the House floor to honor the victims.\"}, {\"start\": 275.0, \"end\": 281.0, \"text\": \"According to the annual \\\"Stress in America\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 286.0, \"text\": \"survey many Americans say that\"}, {\"start\": 286.0, \"end\": 291.0, \"text\": \"the present day is the worst period of American history that they can remember.\"}, {\"start\": 291.0, \"end\": 295.0, \"text\": \"Sixty percent of the adults surveyed said\"}, {\"start\": 295.0, \"end\": 301.0, \"text\": \"the future of the nation is a very significant source of stress for them.\"}, {\"start\": 301.0, \"end\": 306.0, \"text\": \"Money and work were the other causes of stress.\"}, {\"start\": 307.0, \"end\": 310.0, \"text\": \"Women reported higher levels of stress\"}, {\"start\": 310.0, \"end\": 315.0, \"text\": \"than men. The report also found\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 320.0, \"text\": \"that stress caused a majority of people to be inspired to\"}, {\"start\": 320.0, \"end\": 325.0, \"text\": \"do positive things like volunteer or support causes\"}, {\"start\": 326.0, \"end\": 329.0, \"text\": \"that they value.\"}, {\"start\": 334.0, \"end\": 338.0, \"text\": \"The iPhone 10 went on sale today.\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 341.0, \"text\": \"And no surprise -- insanely long lines\"}, {\"start\": 342.0, \"end\": 348.0, \"text\": \"wrapped around the block outside Apple stores worldwide.\"}, {\"start\": 348.0, \"end\": 351.0, \"text\": \"Apparently the new iPhone's $1000 price tag\"}, {\"start\": 351.0, \"end\": 358.0, \"text\": \"is not slowing down demand.\"}, {\"start\": 359.0, \"end\": 365.0, \"text\": \"The new iPhone 10 release came at the same time as Apple's stock\"}, {\"start\": 366.0, \"end\": 371.0, \"text\": \"market value briefly topped nine billion dollars\"}, {\"start\": 371.0, \"end\": 377.0, \"text\": \"for the first time.\"}, {\"start\": 380.0, \"end\": 383.0, \"text\": \"The world champion Houston Astros\"}, {\"start\": 384.0, \"end\": 389.0, \"text\": \"arrived back in Houston today. Team manager AJ  Hinch\"}, {\"start\": 389.0, \"end\": 394.0, \"text\": \"led the team off the plane followed by\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 400.0, \"text\": \"MVP George Springer.\"}, {\"start\": 400.0, \"end\": 406.0, \"text\": \"Springer was carrying the championship trophy.\"}, {\"start\": 407.0, \"end\": 415.0, \"text\": \"Short stop Carlos\"}, {\"start\": 416.0, \"end\": 421.0, \"text\": \"Cabrera walked hand in hand\"}, {\"start\": 421.0, \"end\": 425.0, \"text\": \"with his fiancee. He proposed to her right after the game\"}, {\"start\": 426.0, \"end\": 433.0, \"text\": \"during the championship celebration.\"}, {\"start\": 436.0, \"end\": 439.0, \"text\": \"We want to remind everyone: don't forget\"}, {\"start\": 439.0, \"end\": 445.0, \"text\": \"to set your clock back one hour Saturday night.\"}, {\"start\": 445.0, \"end\": 449.0, \"text\": \"The good news: you will get an extra hour of sleep\"}, {\"start\": 449.0, \"end\": 455.0, \"text\": \"in the morning. The bad news there will be more hours\"}, {\"start\": 455.0, \"end\": 459.0, \"text\": \"of darkness in the evening. Some studies have\"}, {\"start\": 460.0, \"end\": 465.0, \"text\": \"linked the lack of light to depression.\"}, {\"start\": 465.0, \"end\": 470.0, \"text\": \"But experts say there are some things that you can do\"}, {\"start\": 470.0, \"end\": 477.0, \"text\": \"to make the most of your day like\"}, {\"start\": 477.0, \"end\": 483.0, \"text\": \"taking a morning walk right after sunrise.\"}, {\"start\": 483.0, \"end\": 486.0, \"text\": \"Bring more light into your home\"}, {\"start\": 486.0, \"end\": 492.0, \"text\": \"by keeping the blinds and shades open.\"}, {\"start\": 492.0, \"end\": 497.0, \"text\": \"Don't come home to a dark house.\"}, {\"start\": 497.0, \"end\": 501.0, \"text\": \"Buy timers for your lamps and set them\"}, {\"start\": 501.0, \"end\": 506.0, \"text\": \"to turn on before you get home.\"}, {\"start\": 506.0, \"end\": 512.0, \"text\": \"Keep an active social life.\"}, {\"start\": 512.0, \"end\": 519.0, \"text\": \"Plan a winter vacation somewhere nice and sunny.\"}, {\"start\": 519.0, \"end\": 525.0, \"text\": \"Don't oversleep or stay in bed all day.\"}, {\"start\": 525.0, \"end\": 532.0, \"text\": \"And probably most importantly maintain a routine sleep schedule\"}, {\"start\": 532.0, \"end\": 539.0, \"text\": \"so you can keep your body clock on time and get the most out of your day.\"}, {\"start\": 542.0, \"end\": 546.0, \"text\": \"And those are our top stories for today. I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 546.024, \"end\": 548.024, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 549.0, \"end\": 552.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 553.024, \"end\": 558.024, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "f48ZSCY-2MA": {
    "video_id": "f48ZSCY-2MA",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.16.18",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180117",
    "duration": 530,
    "view_count": 1031,
    "description": "1.16.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-California torture house update\n-Winter storm watch from Texas to Maine\n-Three top Trump associates interviewed about Russia\n-Missing mudslide resident found alive, sends selfie\n-Prince Harry, Meghan Markle tv movie in the works\n-CVS bans photoshopped beauty brands\n-Holding in a sneeze can be dangerous\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.26, \"end\": 7.3, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.3, \"end\": 9.42, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.42, \"end\": 10.92, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 10.92, \"end\": 13.88, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.96, \"end\": 26.68, \"text\": \"This is surveillance video, taken from a neighbor's house, of David and Louise Turpin being arrested\"}, {\"start\": 26.68, \"end\": 29.4, \"text\": \"by police.\"}, {\"start\": 29.4, \"end\": 38.16, \"text\": \"They are the California couple accused of torturing and holding their 13 children captive.\"}, {\"start\": 38.16, \"end\": 45.02, \"text\": \"Police say they restrained some of their children to beds with chains and padlocks.\"}, {\"start\": 45.02, \"end\": 49.1, \"text\": \"And they forced them to live in filthy conditions.\"}, {\"start\": 49.1, \"end\": 52.4, \"text\": \"The children range in age from 2 to 29.\"}, {\"start\": 52.4, \"end\": 59.9, \"text\": \"But police say some of the older children were so malnourished they looked like little\"}, {\"start\": 59.9, \"end\": 62.02, \"text\": \"children.\"}, {\"start\": 62.02, \"end\": 67.34, \"text\": \"Police discovered the house of horror after one child, a 17-year-old girl, escaped by\"}, {\"start\": 67.34, \"end\": 70.48, \"text\": \"climbing out of a window calling 9-1-1.\"}, {\"start\": 70.48, \"end\": 79.44, \"text\": \"On social media, however, the Turpins look like a perfectly normal family.\"}, {\"start\": 79.48, \"end\": 87.36, \"text\": \"These are photos of the family, all smiling and wearing matching outfits.\"}, {\"start\": 87.36, \"end\": 92.76, \"text\": \"But neighbors say they never saw the children playing outside.\"}, {\"start\": 92.76, \"end\": 107.36, \"text\": \"The parents have been charged with torture and child endangerment.\"}, {\"start\": 107.36, \"end\": 112.76, \"text\": \"Bail for the couple is set at $9 million each.\"}, {\"start\": 112.779, \"end\": 115.459, \"text\": \"They will have their first court appearance on Thursday.\"}, {\"start\": 115.459, \"end\": 120.76, \"text\": \"All the children are recovering in the hospital.\"}, {\"start\": 122.36, \"end\": 128.4, \"text\": \"Another blast of winter weather is slamming the right side of the United States.\"}, {\"start\": 128.4, \"end\": 136.76, \"text\": \"Snow, ice and bitter cold temperatures have been seen from Texas to Maine.\"}, {\"start\": 136.88, \"end\": 147.48, \"text\": \"In Ohio, Lake Erie has ice 30-feet high in some spots.\"}, {\"start\": 147.6, \"end\": 151.8, \"text\": \"Waterfalls are frozen in South Dakota.\"}, {\"start\": 151.88, \"end\": 158.8, \"text\": \"In Southeast Texas a winter storm warning is in effect through Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 158.8, \"end\": 165.52, \"text\": \"A state of emergency was declared across Alabama Monday night.\"}, {\"start\": 165.52, \"end\": 173.0, \"text\": \"And officials have closed a number of schools in Missouri and Tennessee.\"}, {\"start\": 173.12, \"end\": 181.4, \"text\": \"Other states expected to be affected by this blast are Georgia, West Virginia and Pennsylvania.\"}, {\"start\": 181.56, \"end\": 187.2, \"text\": \"Authorities are urging drivers to be extra careful on the roads and the weather could\"}, {\"start\": 187.2, \"end\": 193.56, \"text\": \"affect flight schedules nationwide.\"}, {\"start\": 195.92, \"end\": 208.04, \"text\": \"Three high-level Trump associates are scheduled to be interviewed this week by the House Intelligence\"}, {\"start\": 208.04, \"end\": 211.32, \"text\": \"panel investigating Russia.\"}, {\"start\": 211.32, \"end\": 220.28, \"text\": \"Former White House chief strategist Steve Bannon met with the panel today.\"}, {\"start\": 220.28, \"end\": 224.64, \"text\": \"He faced several questions about the 2016 presidential campaign.\"}, {\"start\": 224.64, \"end\": 233.16, \"text\": \"Bannon was a top aide in the Trump White House up until last summer when he was fired.\"}, {\"start\": 233.16, \"end\": 238.84, \"text\": \"A source told CNN Bannon retained an attorney to represent him in the closed-door interview.\"}, {\"start\": 238.84, \"end\": 247.28, \"text\": \"White House Communications Director Hope Hicks is also expected to meet separately with the\"}, {\"start\": 247.4, \"end\": 249.16, \"text\": \"same house panel.\"}, {\"start\": 249.36, \"end\": 258.12, \"text\": \"The committee plans to question her knowledge of contacts between Trump associates and Russia.\"}, {\"start\": 258.12, \"end\": 262.4, \"text\": \"She is expected to also be asked about other Trump controversies.\"}, {\"start\": 262.4, \"end\": 273.84, \"text\": \"And former campaign manager Cory Lewandowski is scheduled to testify either Wednesday or\"}, {\"start\": 273.84, \"end\": 276.52, \"text\": \"Thursday.\"}, {\"start\": 278.68, \"end\": 284.6, \"text\": \"There is some good news to report regarding the California mudslides.\"}, {\"start\": 284.6, \"end\": 289.56, \"text\": \"The number of those unaccounted for has gone down from 4 to 3.\"}, {\"start\": 289.56, \"end\": 296.32, \"text\": \"Fifty-three-year-old John \\\"Jack\\\" Keating, who had been listed missing, was found alive\"}, {\"start\": 296.32, \"end\": 299.36, \"text\": \"in Ventura.\"}, {\"start\": 299.36, \"end\": 305.72, \"text\": \"He sent the Sheriff's office this selfie with his dog.\"}, {\"start\": 305.72, \"end\": 315.04, \"text\": \"Searchers are still sifting through debris looking for these three: 17-year-old John\"}, {\"start\": 315.04, \"end\": 336.04, \"text\": \"\\\"Jack\\\" Cantin, 28-year-old Faviola Benitez Calderon and 2-year-old Lydia Sutthithepa.\"}, {\"start\": 336.04, \"end\": 341.88, \"text\": \"Lydia's father and brother were killed in the mudslides.\"}, {\"start\": 343.44, \"end\": 353.68, \"text\": \"Lifetime network is creating a TV movie about the love story of Prince Harry and Meghan\"}, {\"start\": 353.76, \"end\": 358.48, \"text\": \"Markle.\"}, {\"start\": 358.48, \"end\": 371.0, \"text\": \"A network representative shared the plan Sunday at the Television Critics Association winter\"}, {\"start\": 371.0, \"end\": 372.16, \"text\": \"press tour.\"}, {\"start\": 372.16, \"end\": 378.52, \"text\": \"The couple announced their engagement last fall and their wedding date is set for May\"}, {\"start\": 378.62, \"end\": 379.96, \"text\": \"19th.\"}, {\"start\": 379.96, \"end\": 386.0, \"text\": \"The Lifetime representative did not give an official air date but she said the movie should debut\"}, {\"start\": 386.0, \"end\": 388.32, \"text\": \"sometime before the royal wedding.\"}, {\"start\": 390.4, \"end\": 396.86, \"text\": \"On Monday CVS announced the company will eliminate any beauty product images that have been\"}, {\"start\": 396.86, \"end\": 400.42, \"text\": \"photoshopped or altered with touchups.\"}, {\"start\": 400.42, \"end\": 406.44, \"text\": \"The company will no longer promote products where the model's shape, size, skin, eye color\"}, {\"start\": 406.44, \"end\": 412.0, \"text\": \"or wrinkles have been significantly altered.\"}, {\"start\": 412.02, \"end\": 422.7, \"text\": \"Company officials say they want its beauty aisle to be \\\"a place where customers can always\"}, {\"start\": 422.7, \"end\": 423.96, \"text\": \"come to feel good, while representing and celebrating the authenticity and diversity\"}, {\"start\": 423.96, \"end\": 426.12, \"text\": \"of communities they serve.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 426.12, \"end\": 432.28, \"text\": \"The company is also introducing what is called \\\"CVS Beauty Mark\\\" that will be put on photos\"}, {\"start\": 432.36, \"end\": 434.68, \"text\": \"that have not been altered.\"}, {\"start\": 434.68, \"end\": 438.4, \"text\": \"The policy will roll out by the end of 2020.\"}, {\"start\": 441.12, \"end\": 451.16, \"text\": \"According to a new report in the \\\"BMJ Case Reports\\\" medical journal holding in a sneeze\"}, {\"start\": 451.16, \"end\": 453.4, \"text\": \"can be dangerous.\"}, {\"start\": 453.41, \"end\": 458.6, \"text\": \"The report highlights the case of a 34-year-old British man who suffered a neck injury when\"}, {\"start\": 458.6, \"end\": 463.04, \"text\": \"he pinched his nose and kept his mouth closed to hold back a sneeze.\"}, {\"start\": 463.04, \"end\": 466.76, \"text\": \"The force of the suppressed sneeze sent air and other things from the body crashing into\"}, {\"start\": 466.76, \"end\": 468.36, \"text\": \"the back of his throat.\"}, {\"start\": 468.36, \"end\": 477.28, \"text\": \"Doctors found air bubbles into soft tissues and a small tear in his trachea.\"}, {\"start\": 477.4, \"end\": 481.0, \"text\": \"He didn't need surgery but he did have to be hospitalized for two weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 481.0, \"end\": 490.04, \"text\": \"Sneezes can produce pressurized air that can explode at speeds of up to 100 miles an hour.\"}, {\"start\": 490.04, \"end\": 497.44, \"text\": \"So next time you feel a sneeze coming on, doctors say, for the sake of your health,\"}, {\"start\": 497.44, \"end\": 500.32, \"text\": \"let it rip!\"}, {\"start\": 502.12, \"end\": 504.509, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 504.52, \"end\": 506.32, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 506.32, \"end\": 509.16, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 509.16, \"end\": 514.72, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 514.72, \"end\": 521.6, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "zgB-OFgH0m8": {
    "video_id": "zgB-OFgH0m8",
    "title": "Deaf Hip Hop artist Sean Forbes performs in Atlanta (3.24.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180325",
    "duration": 604,
    "view_count": 478,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.22, \"end\": 15.3, \"text\": \"Award-winning deaf rapper Sean Forbes performed in Atlanta earlier this week at Atlanta Area\"}, {\"start\": 15.3, \"end\": 17.06, \"text\": \"School for the Deaf.\"}, {\"start\": 17.06, \"end\": 19.68, \"text\": \"The place was packed!\"}, {\"start\": 19.68, \"end\": 22.9, \"text\": \"Forbes has a huge fan base.\"}, {\"start\": 22.9, \"end\": 33.88, \"text\": \"His message of living \\\"deaf and loud\\\" has impacted and empowered many people.\"}, {\"start\": 33.88, \"end\": 42.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News anchor Jethro Wooddall got an opportunity to sit and chat with Forbes before the show\"}, {\"start\": 42.0, \"end\": 44.78, \"text\": \"to hear his story.\"}, {\"start\": 44.78, \"end\": 48.44, \"text\": \"Enjoy the interview.\"}, {\"start\": 48.44, \"end\": 51.74, \"text\": \"So why are you here performing in Atlanta?\"}, {\"start\": 51.74, \"end\": 56.74, \"text\": \"The school decided to bring me here for two reasons: first to interact with the kids this\"}, {\"start\": 56.74, \"end\": 64.2, \"text\": \"morning and to share my story and life's journey and then to perform for the deaf community.\"}, {\"start\": 64.2, \"end\": 72.54, \"text\": \"The interesting thing is I was right here in this exact room 10 years ago interviewing with CNN.\"}, {\"start\": 72.54, \"end\": 75.56, \"text\": \"So this is really taking me back.\"}, {\"start\": 75.56, \"end\": 76.7, \"text\": \"That's awesome.\"}, {\"start\": 76.7, \"end\": 78.92, \"text\": \"So you're telling me 10 years ago...\"}, {\"start\": 78.92, \"end\": 82.78, \"text\": \"Yes 10 years ago I performed here, similar situation.\"}, {\"start\": 82.82, \"end\": 88.0, \"text\": \"So now 10 years later I feel I have come full circle.\"}, {\"start\": 88.14, \"end\": 92.14, \"text\": \"You blink and you're back.\"}, {\"start\": 92.14, \"end\": 98.02, \"text\": \"So how did you develop this dream of becoming a rapper?\"}, {\"start\": 98.02, \"end\": 100.5, \"text\": \"Really it just happened.\"}, {\"start\": 100.5, \"end\": 103.22, \"text\": \"Growing up I was always fascinated with music.\"}, {\"start\": 103.22, \"end\": 108.92, \"text\": \"I always wanted to write songs, play drums, just have fun with music.\"}, {\"start\": 108.92, \"end\": 113.28, \"text\": \"I really didn't start rapping until I was about 12 or 13 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 113.28, \"end\": 114.54, \"text\": \"I was blown away by it.\"}, {\"start\": 114.54, \"end\": 123.86, \"text\": \"When I was growing up my parents and two brothers loved rock, acid rock and heavy metal.\"}, {\"start\": 125.42, \"end\": 127.22, \"text\": \"It was really different when I was growing up.\"}, {\"start\": 127.22, \"end\": 133.96, \"text\": \"But when I discovered rap music, it truly spoke to me for a number of reasons.\"}, {\"start\": 133.96, \"end\": 142.24, \"text\": \"One, rap has a rhythm and since I'm a drummer (I've been drumming since I was five)... so\"}, {\"start\": 142.24, \"end\": 149.58, \"text\": \"with the rhythm and drums, I feel like rap just really resonated with me.\"}, {\"start\": 149.58, \"end\": 152.9, \"text\": \"So you are truly feeling the rhythm?\"}, {\"start\": 152.9, \"end\": 158.98, \"text\": \"So your parents love classic rock but your sister...\"}, {\"start\": 158.98, \"end\": 161.7, \"text\": \"No I have two brothers.\"}, {\"start\": 161.7, \"end\": 164.04, \"text\": \"Okay I'm not gonna question their preference of music.\"}, {\"start\": 164.04, \"end\": 165.4, \"text\": \"I think I'm going to stick to the rap.\"}, {\"start\": 165.4, \"end\": 166.96, \"text\": \"I love heavy metal.\"}, {\"start\": 167.08, \"end\": 172.82, \"text\": \"I like all music and respect all genres.\"}, {\"start\": 172.82, \"end\": 177.56, \"text\": \"People always ask me what do I have a preference for and honestly I like art.\"}, {\"start\": 177.56, \"end\": 180.48, \"text\": \"I listen, experience and feel.\"}, {\"start\": 180.48, \"end\": 182.38, \"text\": \"Music about feeling.\"}, {\"start\": 182.38, \"end\": 185.76, \"text\": \"Sometimes people take it too literally.\"}, {\"start\": 185.76, \"end\": 187.62, \"text\": \"Like \\\"feeling.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 187.62, \"end\": 192.72, \"text\": \"I'm talking about connecting with what the artist is saying.\"}, {\"start\": 192.72, \"end\": 197.92, \"text\": \"When I started signing music, I started with other artists' songs so people could understand\"}, {\"start\": 197.92, \"end\": 200.3, \"text\": \"what the artist was saying.\"}, {\"start\": 200.3, \"end\": 210.94, \"text\": \"Like right now, before this performance, that Matt Maxey, he is really expressing the culture.\"}, {\"start\": 210.94, \"end\": 212.84, \"text\": \"I really love that music.\"}, {\"start\": 212.84, \"end\": 218.72, \"text\": \"So for me, I see what he is doing and what I was doing 10 years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 218.72, \"end\": 226.2, \"text\": \"I feel he's really expressing the artist within.\"}, {\"start\": 226.2, \"end\": 232.4, \"text\": \"Matt has that swag, that personality so I applaud him.\"}, {\"start\": 232.48, \"end\": 234.86, \"text\": \"I'm a big fan.\"}, {\"start\": 235.64, \"end\": 238.7, \"text\": \"So let's talk about you loving all artists and genres of music.\"}, {\"start\": 238.7, \"end\": 239.28, \"text\": \"I'm curious.\"}, {\"start\": 239.28, \"end\": 240.74, \"text\": \"What about country music?\"}, {\"start\": 240.74, \"end\": 242.24, \"text\": \"I love country music!\"}, {\"start\": 242.24, \"end\": 243.86, \"text\": \"Oh yes.\"}, {\"start\": 243.86, \"end\": 244.62, \"text\": \"I love country music.\"}, {\"start\": 244.62, \"end\": 248.36, \"text\": \"My father worked for a country music group.\"}, {\"start\": 248.36, \"end\": 256.7, \"text\": \"So I grew up with country music, the Eagles, all those guys.\"}, {\"start\": 257.34, \"end\": 261.58, \"text\": \"Okay so what do you mean you been rapping for 10 years now?\"}, {\"start\": 263.8, \"end\": 265.78, \"text\": \"Okay well... let me go back.\"}, {\"start\": 265.92, \"end\": 268.6, \"text\": \"I discovered rap when I was about 12 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 268.6, \"end\": 275.2, \"text\": \"I didn't start signing until I was 10 or 11 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 275.2, \"end\": 280.02, \"text\": \"I really didn't start signing rap until I was in college at RIT.\"}, {\"start\": 280.02, \"end\": 291.18, \"text\": \"It was really kind of awkward but my skills have evolved over the past 10 years.\"}, {\"start\": 291.18, \"end\": 294.68, \"text\": \"I feel like when I was watching a video of myself it's like...\"}, {\"start\": 294.68, \"end\": 295.94, \"text\": \"Now you know how I feel!\"}, {\"start\": 295.949, \"end\": 298.05, \"text\": \"I feel that way all the time with my signing.\"}, {\"start\": 298.05, \"end\": 304.039, \"text\": \"When I recorded myself sign here at Atlanta Area School for the Deaf and...so I know how\"}, {\"start\": 304.04, \"end\": 306.68, \"text\": \"you feel.\"}, {\"start\": 306.68, \"end\": 309.86, \"text\": \"So you been in the rap game for about 10 years.\"}, {\"start\": 309.86, \"end\": 311.72, \"text\": \"How many albums do you have?\"}, {\"start\": 311.72, \"end\": 313.88, \"text\": \"I've only put out one album.\"}, {\"start\": 313.88, \"end\": 315.2, \"text\": \"Just one.\"}, {\"start\": 315.2, \"end\": 316.66, \"text\": \"I thought there were several albums.\"}, {\"start\": 316.66, \"end\": 317.66, \"text\": \"No just the one.\"}, {\"start\": 317.66, \"end\": 321.02, \"text\": \"I put out several different songs but only one album.\"}, {\"start\": 321.02, \"end\": 322.82, \"text\": \"But I have a little bit of news to share.\"}, {\"start\": 322.82, \"end\": 325.42, \"text\": \"I just finished a new album.\"}, {\"start\": 325.42, \"end\": 327.08, \"text\": \"I just finished two weeks ago.\"}, {\"start\": 327.08, \"end\": 329.78, \"text\": \"It is ready to be released soon.\"}, {\"start\": 329.78, \"end\": 331.42, \"text\": \"That is exciting news!\"}, {\"start\": 331.42, \"end\": 337.08, \"text\": \"I've finished making the music, writing songs and now I'm working on the music video because\"}, {\"start\": 337.08, \"end\": 340.12, \"text\": \"I believe music should be accessible for everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 340.12, \"end\": 342.12, \"text\": \"I want hearing people to enjoy it.\"}, {\"start\": 342.12, \"end\": 346.24, \"text\": \"The goal of this album is more visual.\"}, {\"start\": 346.24, \"end\": 353.24, \"text\": \"When hearing people listen to music they can visualize and imagine.\"}, {\"start\": 353.24, \"end\": 360.64, \"text\": \"For me, my last album, it was visual also but visual in a way that you could see what\"}, {\"start\": 360.64, \"end\": 362.98, \"text\": \"the song means.\"}, {\"start\": 362.98, \"end\": 368.12, \"text\": \"The way I make music videos you can see what I'm saying this time.\"}, {\"start\": 368.12, \"end\": 377.7, \"text\": \"I wanted to show the music, show my ASL, show my expression, to show what it looks like.\"}, {\"start\": 377.7, \"end\": 381.08, \"text\": \"I know it's a little bit far out.\"}, {\"start\": 381.08, \"end\": 383.7, \"text\": \"I'm so looking forward to that.\"}, {\"start\": 383.8, \"end\": 384.64, \"text\": \"Can't wait to see it.\"}, {\"start\": 384.82, \"end\": 386.98, \"text\": \"That's exciting.\"}, {\"start\": 386.98, \"end\": 390.7, \"text\": \"Do you write and sign your own songs?\"}, {\"start\": 390.7, \"end\": 399.66, \"text\": \"I write my own lyrics but also work with a producer named Jake Bass who writes music.\"}, {\"start\": 399.66, \"end\": 406.26, \"text\": \"For this album and the last one I was involved with every song from the start.\"}, {\"start\": 406.26, \"end\": 415.46, \"text\": \"For example, for a new song I would play the drums and then write.\"}, {\"start\": 415.46, \"end\": 421.22, \"text\": \"It was an interesting process for me because on the last album Jake gave me all the music\"}, {\"start\": 421.22, \"end\": 425.08, \"text\": \"and I got to pick which ones I liked.\"}, {\"start\": 425.08, \"end\": 427.98, \"text\": \"Really I like everything he makes.\"}, {\"start\": 427.98, \"end\": 435.84, \"text\": \"He's made over 100 different songs so you become very selective with the song you put out.\"}, {\"start\": 439.42, \"end\": 452.82, \"text\": \"So now that you are in Atlanta what message do you have for children who have big dreams?\"}, {\"start\": 452.82, \"end\": 455.78, \"text\": \"Well the journey is not always what you expect.\"}, {\"start\": 455.78, \"end\": 458.6, \"text\": \"You have to expect the unexpected.\"}, {\"start\": 458.6, \"end\": 462.4, \"text\": \"For example my journey, I really wanted to arrive on the music scene but my journey is\"}, {\"start\": 462.4, \"end\": 465.18, \"text\": \"taking me everywhere, to different places.\"}, {\"start\": 465.2, \"end\": 471.8, \"text\": \"I established DPAN-TV to make music accessible and that is a challenge.\"}, {\"start\": 471.8, \"end\": 477.42, \"text\": \"The music business doesn't really understand where the deaf community is coming from.\"}, {\"start\": 477.5, \"end\": 481.72, \"text\": \"It would be nice to see Matt continue his journey with DPAN-TV.\"}, {\"start\": 481.72, \"end\": 485.9, \"text\": \"I really want to make a platform for signing content.\"}, {\"start\": 485.9, \"end\": 494.4, \"text\": \"That's really my goal with DPAN-TV because I feel like, for DPan, all of our music is\"}, {\"start\": 494.4, \"end\": 496.86, \"text\": \"released through YouTube.\"}, {\"start\": 496.86, \"end\": 503.42, \"text\": \"And that's a little sad because we spend so much time and energy on those videos, a lot\"}, {\"start\": 503.42, \"end\": 511.88, \"text\": \"of money, and when you search for your favorite video, YouTube has a zillion other videos show up.\"}, {\"start\": 511.88, \"end\": 515.02, \"text\": \"You don't know what's good and what's bad.\"}, {\"start\": 515.02, \"end\": 522.64, \"text\": \"So sometimes I feel is not beneficial for those who want to learn a language.\"}, {\"start\": 522.64, \"end\": 528.3, \"text\": \"It's it's like \\\"Oh I saw this cool video\\\" but the signing is awful.\"}, {\"start\": 528.52, \"end\": 533.78, \"text\": \"I'm in favor of people learning our language.\"}, {\"start\": 533.78, \"end\": 535.1, \"text\": \"Of course.\"}, {\"start\": 535.1, \"end\": 540.94, \"text\": \"But at the same time there needs to be a level of respect as well.\"}, {\"start\": 542.02, \"end\": 548.54, \"text\": \"It's just with DPAN-TV everything were doing is about trying to be original.\"}, {\"start\": 550.12, \"end\": 559.0, \"text\": \"So bottom line, your message is to expect the unexpected and be original.\"}, {\"start\": 559.0, \"end\": 560.78, \"text\": \"Be original! Yes!\"}, {\"start\": 560.88, \"end\": 562.82, \"text\": \"I like that.\"}, {\"start\": 562.82, \"end\": 565.24, \"text\": \"Thank you for taking the time to sit and chat.\"}, {\"start\": 565.24, \"end\": 566.8, \"text\": \"I know you have to go and get ready to perform.\"}, {\"start\": 566.8, \"end\": 567.82, \"text\": \"I hope you enjoy the show tonight.\"}, {\"start\": 567.82, \"end\": 568.88, \"text\": \"Oh you know I will.\"}, {\"start\": 568.88, \"end\": 569.86, \"text\": \"If he stays.\"}, {\"start\": 569.86, \"end\": 575.9, \"text\": \"Maybe he so busy he's got a jet off to interview another person, I don't know.\"}, {\"start\": 576.18, \"end\": 579.3, \"text\": \"Okay truth be told, I'm your number one fan.\"}, {\"start\": 579.36, \"end\": 580.56, \"text\": \"Don't tell them.\"}, {\"start\": 580.56, \"end\": 582.8, \"text\": \"You will see him on the front row rockin' out.\"}, {\"start\": 582.8, \"end\": 586.0, \"text\": \"It's more like this, not this.\"}, {\"start\": 586.4, \"end\": 589.6, \"text\": \"I like this.\"}, {\"start\": 589.6, \"end\": 591.84, \"text\": \"I'll remember that next time.\"}, {\"start\": 591.84, \"end\": 592.72, \"text\": \"Thank you.\"}, {\"start\": 594.8, \"end\": 598.96, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching my interview with Sean Forbes.\"}, {\"start\": 598.96, \"end\": 601.58, \"text\": \"Back to you in the Sign1News studio.\"}, {\"start\": 601.58, \"end\": 603.58, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}]"
  },
  "jj-nKpL4mWQ": {
    "video_id": "jj-nKpL4mWQ",
    "title": "Prince Harry, Meghan Markle new wedding details (ASL - 2.12.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180213",
    "duration": 68,
    "view_count": 124,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.2, \"end\": 13.42, \"text\": \"Kensington Palace has announced new details about the wedding of Prince Harry and Meghan\"}, {\"start\": 13.42, \"end\": 15.12, \"text\": \"Markle.\"}, {\"start\": 15.12, \"end\": 20.68, \"text\": \"The couple will marry at noon local time on May 19th.\"}, {\"start\": 20.68, \"end\": 25.74, \"text\": \"That's 7 AM Eastern in the US.\"}, {\"start\": 25.8, \"end\": 34.68, \"text\": \"The wedding will take place in St. George's Chapel at Windsor Castle.\"}, {\"start\": 34.68, \"end\": 43.22, \"text\": \"The palace also announced the couple will undertake a carriage procession.\"}, {\"start\": 43.22, \"end\": 49.32, \"text\": \"The carriage will go through the town of Windsor and then returned to the castle.\"}, {\"start\": 49.32, \"end\": 57.96, \"text\": \"The couple will also hold their wedding reception in Windsor Castle with the Prince of Wales\"}, {\"start\": 58.04, \"end\": 65.84, \"text\": \"hosting a private party for close friends and family later in the evening.\"}]"
  },
  "OLkLPPWE4Ks": {
    "video_id": "OLkLPPWE4Ks",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.19.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171020",
    "duration": 425,
    "view_count": 117,
    "description": "October 19, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-UNIV OF FL STUDENTS PROTEST WHITE NATIONALIST'S SPEECH\n-PROTESTS SPILL INTO STREET\n-TRUMP MEETS WITH PUERTO RICO GOVERNOR\n-FOOD DISTRIBUTED TO 400 RESIDENTS IN PUERTO RICO\n-JOBLESS CLAIMS LOWEST SINCE 1973\n-TRASH TALKING BROTHERS\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 11.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.0, \"end\": 15.0, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau. And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.0, \"end\": 23.0, \"text\": \"Today dozens of University of\"}, {\"start\": 23.0, \"end\": 31.0, \"text\": \"Florida students protested because Richard Spencer,\"}, {\"start\": 31.0, \"end\": 39.0, \"text\": \"a white supremacist, was speaking on campus.\"}, {\"start\": 39.0, \"end\": 43.9, \"text\": \"The students were very upset that the school allowed him to speak.\"}, {\"start\": 44.0, \"end\": 47.0, \"text\": \"The school's president said the school\"}, {\"start\": 47.0, \"end\": 54.0, \"text\": \"is required to allow Spencer to speak on\"}, {\"start\": 54.0, \"end\": 59.0, \"text\": \"campus because of free speech laws.\"}, {\"start\": 59.0, \"end\": 64.0, \"text\": \"But he advised students and staff to stay away\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 69.0, \"text\": \"from the event. He said Spencer's\"}, {\"start\": 69.0, \"end\": 76.0, \"text\": \"ideals are not part of Gator Nation.\"}, {\"start\": 76.0, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"Student protesters showed up anyway. They booed and\"}, {\"start\": 81.0, \"end\": 87.0, \"text\": \"shouted the entire time Spencer was speaking.\"}, {\"start\": 87.0, \"end\": 92.0, \"text\": \"The event was heavily guarded with police. The\"}, {\"start\": 92.0, \"end\": 97.0, \"text\": \"speech ended without incident.\"}, {\"start\": 100.0, \"end\": 104.0, \"text\": \"When Spencer's speech ended the scene was different\"}, {\"start\": 107.0, \"end\": 111.0, \"text\": \"outside the auditorium. Hundreds of\"}, {\"start\": 111.0, \"end\": 115.0, \"text\": \"student protesters clashed with\"}, {\"start\": 116.0, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"Spencer's supporters. They were also hundreds of\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 123.0, \"text\": \"police trying to keep the peace.\"}, {\"start\": 123.0, \"end\": 128.0, \"text\": \"The school's president said there was more police on campus than\"}, {\"start\": 128.0, \"end\": 133.0, \"text\": \"at any time in the university's history.\"}, {\"start\": 133.0, \"end\": 138.0, \"text\": \"The school spent more than five hundred thousand dollars\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 143.0, \"text\": \"to beef up security and prevent major problems.\"}, {\"start\": 145.0, \"end\": 150.0, \"text\": \"Today President Trump traveled to Puerto Rico\"}, {\"start\": 150.0, \"end\": 155.0, \"text\": \"to meet with government leaders.\"}, {\"start\": 155.0, \"end\": 162.0, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico's governor Ricardo Rosello\"}, {\"start\": 162.0, \"end\": 167.0, \"text\": \"says all he wants is a quick response\"}, {\"start\": 167.0, \"end\": 171.0, \"text\": \"for aid, services and support\"}, {\"start\": 172.0, \"end\": 176.0, \"text\": \"and to explain the pressing needs of residents.\"}, {\"start\": 176.0, \"end\": 180.0, \"text\": \"A few weeks back President Trump was heavily criticized\"}, {\"start\": 182.0, \"end\": 190.0, \"text\": \"for tweeting that Washington couldn't keep aiding Puerto Rico forever.\"}, {\"start\": 190.0, \"end\": 194.0, \"text\": \"Last month Trump said\"}, {\"start\": 195.0, \"end\": 199.0, \"text\": \"Hurricane Maria wasn't a real catastrophe\"}, {\"start\": 199.0, \"end\": 204.0, \"text\": \"like Hurricane Katrina because more people died during\"}, {\"start\": 204.0, \"end\": 209.0, \"text\": \"Hurricane Katrina than Hurricane Maria. But today\"}, {\"start\": 209.0, \"end\": 213.0, \"text\": \"he flipped his comments saying the devastation in Puerto\"}, {\"start\": 214.0, \"end\": 218.0, \"text\": \"Rico was worse than in New Orleans during Hurricane Katrina.\"}, {\"start\": 222.0, \"end\": 230.0, \"text\": \"Aid is slowly getting to the hardest hit areas in\"}, {\"start\": 231.0, \"end\": 235.0, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico. This is video from the city\"}, {\"start\": 236.0, \"end\": 241.0, \"text\": \"Canovanas, which is about 20 miles east\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 248.0, \"text\": \"of San Juan. Roughly 400 people live there.\"}, {\"start\": 248.1, \"end\": 251.1, \"text\": \"The video shows members of\"}, {\"start\": 251.1, \"end\": 256.0, \"text\": \"the Coast Guard, FEMA, the army and members of a Puerto\"}, {\"start\": 256.0, \"end\": 262.0, \"text\": \"Rico organization delivering food and water.\"}, {\"start\": 262.024, \"end\": 268.024, \"text\": \"This group has been delivering aid to areas in need for about three weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 268.2, \"end\": 272.0, \"text\": \"About 1 million people still don't have\"}, {\"start\": 272.0, \"end\": 276.7, \"text\": \"clean drinking water. More than 80\"}, {\"start\": 277.0, \"end\": 281.0, \"text\": \"percent of the residents don't have power. In total\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 284.0, \"text\": \"that's about three million people.\"}, {\"start\": 287.0, \"end\": 290.0, \"text\": \"New statistics show the\"}, {\"start\": 291.0, \"end\": 296.0, \"text\": \"American job market is improving. The federal government\"}, {\"start\": 296.0, \"end\": 301.0, \"text\": \"says last week about 222-thousand Americans filed first time\"}, {\"start\": 301.0, \"end\": 306.0, \"text\": \"unemployment claims. That's the lowest number recorded\"}, {\"start\": 306.0, \"end\": 310.0, \"text\": \"in over 43 years. Unemployment is already at a 16 year\"}, {\"start\": 310.0, \"end\": 316.0, \"text\": \"low at four point two percent.\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 322.0, \"text\": \"Experts say the news is another\"}, {\"start\": 322.0, \"end\": 326.0, \"text\": \"sign of a healthy U.S. economy.\"}, {\"start\": 326.0, \"end\": 333.0, \"text\": \"But the economy did lose 33-thousand jobs in September\"}, {\"start\": 333.0, \"end\": 339.0, \"text\": \"which experts blame on three hurricanes taking aim on the U.S.\"}, {\"start\": 342.9, \"end\": 347.9, \"text\": \"In North Dakota two brothers\"}, {\"start\": 347.9, \"end\": 351.0, \"text\": \"ages 2 and 4\"}, {\"start\": 351.2, \"end\": 357.2, \"text\": \"dream of one day becoming garbagemen.\"}, {\"start\": 357.2, \"end\": 365.2, \"text\": \"So the workers at West Fargo sanitation\"}, {\"start\": 365.2, \"end\": 372.9, \"text\": \"allowed the boys to live out their dreams for one day.\"}, {\"start\": 373.0, \"end\": 378.0, \"text\": \"They got to push all the buttons on the truck, haul garbage bins\"}, {\"start\": 378.0, \"end\": 383.0, \"text\": \"to the dump and honk the horn on the truck.\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 388.0, \"text\": \"And the hats and the vests they were wearing are not just for one day.\"}, {\"start\": 388.0, \"end\": 392.0, \"text\": \"The clothes will actually be their Halloween costumes this year.\"}, {\"start\": 395.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 398.0, \"end\": 402.0, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 402.0, \"end\": 409.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 409.0, \"end\": 417.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "DesJoWoUrDU": {
    "video_id": "DesJoWoUrDU",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.18.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180319",
    "duration": 623,
    "view_count": 1506,
    "description": "3.18.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Sign1News anchor Candace Jones signs National Anthem\n-Miami bridge collapse: six vehicles recovered\n-McCabe offered job to save pension\n-Comey book will be released in April, already best seller\n-Little Caesars gives away free lunch combo on April 2\n-Sonic to sell pickle juice slushies \n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.02, \"end\": 8.3, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.3, \"end\": 10.32, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.32, \"end\": 11.76, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.84, \"end\": 15.76, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.16, \"end\": 30.42, \"text\": \"We want to congratulate Sign1News anchor Candace Jones!\"}, {\"start\": 30.42, \"end\": 42.84, \"text\": \"She stood in front of 60,000 soccer fans and signed the US and Canadian national anthem\"}, {\"start\": 42.84, \"end\": 62.08, \"text\": \"at the Atlanta United-Vancouver Whitecaps game Saturday night at Mercedes-Benz Stadium.\"}, {\"start\": 62.08, \"end\": 73.82, \"text\": \"Some team officials say her rendition was one of the best interpretations they've ever seen.\"}, {\"start\": 74.08, \"end\": 83.86, \"text\": \"Jones said she was a little nervous before she started but really got into it once the\"}, {\"start\": 83.86, \"end\": 87.14, \"text\": \"song started.\"}, {\"start\": 87.14, \"end\": 96.6, \"text\": \"Afterwards she said she was honored to be a role model for the Deaf community, especially\"}, {\"start\": 96.6, \"end\": 100.24, \"text\": \"for young people.\"}, {\"start\": 100.34, \"end\": 104.78, \"text\": \"It feels wonderful to be a role model for the deaf community and to show the hearing\"}, {\"start\": 104.78, \"end\": 109.46, \"text\": \"world that Deaf people can interpret music even if they can't hear the words.\"}, {\"start\": 109.46, \"end\": 112.76, \"text\": \"They see how we express music through signs and facial expressions.\"}, {\"start\": 112.76, \"end\": 119.92, \"text\": \"This week my students told me they were going to watch the Atlanta United game with their families.\"}, {\"start\": 119.92, \"end\": 123.62, \"text\": \"When I told them I was going to be at the game signing the national anthem, they were\"}, {\"start\": 123.62, \"end\": 128.56, \"text\": \"so excited!\"}, {\"start\": 128.56, \"end\": 132.76, \"text\": \"So instead of just watching someone singing the national anthem, they actually got to\"}, {\"start\": 132.76, \"end\": 138.16, \"text\": \"see someone, me, their teacher, signing in their language.\"}, {\"start\": 138.16, \"end\": 140.28, \"text\": \"It was fabulous!\"}, {\"start\": 141.96, \"end\": 148.4, \"text\": \"Jones may have been the team's good luck charm too.\"}, {\"start\": 148.4, \"end\": 152.56, \"text\": \"Atlanta beat Vancouver 4-1.\"}, {\"start\": 152.56, \"end\": 159.48, \"text\": \"If you missed Jones' performance, you can see it in its entirety on our Facebook page\"}, {\"start\": 159.48, \"end\": 163.52, \"text\": \"as well as behind-the-scenes footage.\"}, {\"start\": 163.52, \"end\": 166.64, \"text\": \"Again congratulations Candace.\"}, {\"start\": 170.28, \"end\": 176.56, \"text\": \"In Florida recovery workers have pulled six vehicles from the rubble of the collapsed\"}, {\"start\": 176.56, \"end\": 178.96, \"text\": \"pedestrian bridge.\"}, {\"start\": 178.96, \"end\": 188.24, \"text\": \"Officials say two cars were pulled out today with one body in one car and two bodies in\"}, {\"start\": 188.32, \"end\": 190.24, \"text\": \"the other.\"}, {\"start\": 190.24, \"end\": 196.6, \"text\": \"At least two bodies and four cars remain buried in the rubble.\"}, {\"start\": 196.6, \"end\": 202.68, \"text\": \"Crews hope to finish search and recovery efforts this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 202.72, \"end\": 210.36, \"text\": \"Rescuers say they are bracing themselves to find more victims than initially suspected.\"}, {\"start\": 210.44, \"end\": 217.8, \"text\": \"And rescuers are not just removing the bodies; they are honoring the victims as well.\"}, {\"start\": 221.6, \"end\": 229.56, \"text\": \"Every time a body is removed, rescuers stop everything and stand in silence as the body\"}, {\"start\": 229.56, \"end\": 233.36, \"text\": \"is taken away.\"}, {\"start\": 235.76, \"end\": 249.12, \"text\": \"On Friday night Attorney General Jeff Sessions fired former FBI director Andrew McCabe.\"}, {\"start\": 249.12, \"end\": 251.88, \"text\": \"The firing came before McCabe's 50th birthday,\"}, {\"start\": 251.88, \"end\": 255.08, \"text\": \"when he could legally begin collecting his pension.\"}, {\"start\": 255.08, \"end\": 265.84, \"text\": \"On Saturday, several Democratic representatives said McCabe had earned his pension and tweeted\"}, {\"start\": 265.84, \"end\": 271.96, \"text\": \"him with job offers to help him qualify for his full pension.\"}, {\"start\": 271.96, \"end\": 279.32, \"text\": \"Many Democrats say McCabe was clearly fired for political reasons.\"}, {\"start\": 279.32, \"end\": 292.28, \"text\": \"President Trump has accused McCabe of allowing a pro-liberal bias to contaminate the FBI's work.\"}, {\"start\": 292.28, \"end\": 300.84, \"text\": \"But McCabe is reportedly a lifelong Republican who voted in the Republican primary in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 304.24, \"end\": 320.64, \"text\": \"Former FBI director James Comey's book \\\"A Higher Loyalty\\\" won't be released until April 17.\"}, {\"start\": 320.64, \"end\": 330.66, \"text\": \"But as of Sunday morning, it was number two on Amazon's bestseller list.\"}, {\"start\": 330.66, \"end\": 337.76, \"text\": \"President Trump slammed Comey on Twitter when he heard about the book, hinting that the\"}, {\"start\": 337.76, \"end\": 347.92, \"text\": \"FBI was full of lies and corruption under Comey's watch.\"}, {\"start\": 347.92, \"end\": 356.18, \"text\": \"Comey immediately fired back on Twitter saying: \\\"Mr. President, the American people will hear\"}, {\"start\": 356.18, \"end\": 358.26, \"text\": \"my story very soon.\"}, {\"start\": 358.26, \"end\": 364.66, \"text\": \"And they can judge for themselves who is honorable and who is not.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 364.66, \"end\": 371.74, \"text\": \"His retort has been shared more than 100,000 times, making it twice as popular as Trump's\"}, {\"start\": 371.74, \"end\": 374.68, \"text\": \"original tweet.\"}, {\"start\": 374.88, \"end\": 383.26, \"text\": \"And by Sunday morning, pre-orders for Comey's book had him near the top of Amazon's list.\"}, {\"start\": 383.26, \"end\": 391.08, \"text\": \"But that's not the only seller that showed a surge of pre-order sales over the weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 391.08, \"end\": 402.42, \"text\": \"It was also number four on Barnes &amp; Noble's list of best-selling books on Sunday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 407.48, \"end\": 416.92, \"text\": \"When the NCAA men's basketball tournament started earlier this week, Little Caesars\"}, {\"start\": 416.92, \"end\": 424.92, \"text\": \"pizza announced it would do a pizza giveaway if a number 16 seed team beat a number one seed.\"}, {\"start\": 424.92, \"end\": 433.36, \"text\": \"Understand no 16 seed team had ever beaten a number one seed in the tournament's history.\"}, {\"start\": 433.36, \"end\": 436.94, \"text\": \"That is until Friday night.\"}, {\"start\": 436.94, \"end\": 451.44, \"text\": \"The University of Maryland-Baltimore County beat the University of Virginia 74 to 54.\"}, {\"start\": 451.44, \"end\": 460.16, \"text\": \"Little Caesars says it is going to stick to its promise.\"}, {\"start\": 460.16, \"end\": 467.68, \"text\": \"The franchise is going to be providing a free, five dollar lunchbox on Monday, April 2 between\"}, {\"start\": 467.68, \"end\": 472.1, \"text\": \"11:30 AM and 1 PM local time.\"}, {\"start\": 472.12, \"end\": 475.52, \"text\": \"There are some details you want to know about though.\"}, {\"start\": 475.52, \"end\": 485.62, \"text\": \"The deal ends promptly at 1 PM, so if you're still in line and haven't ordered, you'll\"}, {\"start\": 485.62, \"end\": 487.98, \"text\": \"have to pay.\"}, {\"start\": 487.98, \"end\": 497.08, \"text\": \"And there is only one free box lunch box per order, so it will be best to order individually.\"}, {\"start\": 498.64, \"end\": 515.86, \"text\": \"Sonic believes America is ready to wash down their burgers with some frozen pickle juice.\"}, {\"start\": 515.86, \"end\": 519.04, \"text\": \"The fast food chain plans to unveil a pickle juice slushie for a limited time starting\"}, {\"start\": 519.04, \"end\": 521.58, \"text\": \"this June.\"}, {\"start\": 521.58, \"end\": 526.38, \"text\": \"As the name suggests, the drink is a snowcone-like beverage flavored with pickle juice and\"}, {\"start\": 526.38, \"end\": 530.94, \"text\": \"colored bright green.\"}, {\"start\": 530.94, \"end\": 538.66, \"text\": \"The drink is already getting a thumbs up from the people at \\\"Food and Wine\\\" magazine.\"}, {\"start\": 538.66, \"end\": 546.64, \"text\": \"They say it is, quote, \\\"surprisingly delicious\\\" as well as \\\"sweet and tangy.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 546.7, \"end\": 553.38, \"text\": \"And Sonic's pickle juice obsession won't be limited to slushies.\"}, {\"start\": 553.38, \"end\": 561.44, \"text\": \"Sonic will allow customers to request pickle juice on any menu item.\"}, {\"start\": 561.44, \"end\": 571.36, \"text\": \"That means customers can add pickle juice to their burgers, tater tots, even sundaes!\"}, {\"start\": 571.36, \"end\": 573.58, \"text\": \"I personally love pickle juice.\"}, {\"start\": 573.58, \"end\": 575.28, \"text\": \"Maybe you do too.\"}, {\"start\": 575.28, \"end\": 577.58, \"text\": \"What do you think?\"}, {\"start\": 577.58, \"end\": 582.96, \"text\": \"Will pickle juice slushies be the next great fast food item?\"}, {\"start\": 583.12, \"end\": 590.7, \"text\": \"Type or video tape your comments on our Facebook page and we'll share some of your thoughts\"}, {\"start\": 590.7, \"end\": 595.08, \"text\": \"in the show tomorrow.\"}, {\"start\": 598.12, \"end\": 600.64, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 600.64, \"end\": 602.12, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 602.12, \"end\": 604.68, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 604.68, \"end\": 609.14, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 609.18, \"end\": 615.4, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "MXdPJj8gNOQ": {
    "video_id": "MXdPJj8gNOQ",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.16.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180316",
    "duration": 529,
    "view_count": 1264,
    "description": "3.16.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Update: Deadly Miami bridge collapse\n-Bridge collapse memorials grow\n-FIU bridge builder fined for 2012 collapse in Virginia\n-LSU frat hazing death, 4 indictments\n-Jennifer Lopez speaking out on being sexually harassed\n-Get some rest! “It’s World Sleep Day”\n-California zoos welcome baby giraffe and meerkat mob\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news lead",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.96, \"end\": 7.98, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.98, \"end\": 9.84, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.84, \"end\": 11.54, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.54, \"end\": 15.12, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.74, \"end\": 24.62, \"text\": \"The Miami pedestrian bridge rescue operation is now a recovery operation.\"}, {\"start\": 24.62, \"end\": 31.76, \"text\": \"Of the six people killed, five bodies are still under the bridge wreckage.\"}, {\"start\": 31.76, \"end\": 39.72, \"text\": \"Officials say their priority now is getting to those remains so they can be taken to a\"}, {\"start\": 39.72, \"end\": 42.94, \"text\": \"proper place of rest.\"}, {\"start\": 42.94, \"end\": 48.04, \"text\": \"The National Transportation Safety Board is on the scene and in the very early stages\"}, {\"start\": 48.04, \"end\": 51.02, \"text\": \"of its investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 51.02, \"end\": 57.44, \"text\": \"Its number one goal is to find out what caused the bridge to collapse so that it doesn't\"}, {\"start\": 57.44, \"end\": 65.84, \"text\": \"happen again and to find out who's responsible.\"}, {\"start\": 65.84, \"end\": 72.32, \"text\": \"The walkway had only been in place a couple of days and was supposed to be completed over\"}, {\"start\": 72.32, \"end\": 75.06, \"text\": \"the next few months.\"}, {\"start\": 75.06, \"end\": 86.3, \"text\": \"Florida Governor Rick Scott said \\\"If anybody has done anything wrong, we will hold them\"}, {\"start\": 86.3, \"end\": 90.04, \"text\": \"accountable.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 93.2, \"end\": 100.64, \"text\": \"Overnight people started coming to the intersection where the bridge collapsed to light candles\"}, {\"start\": 100.64, \"end\": 106.3, \"text\": \"for those killed and for the ones still trapped under the rubble.\"}, {\"start\": 106.3, \"end\": 113.98, \"text\": \"As you can see many people just sat in silence, some prayed, some cried.\"}, {\"start\": 113.98, \"end\": 119.86, \"text\": \"And this picture was taken from up above.\"}, {\"start\": 119.86, \"end\": 128.02, \"text\": \"Someone placed their candles in the shape of a heart to honor those killed.\"}, {\"start\": 130.5, \"end\": 140.98, \"text\": \"One of the builders of the pedestrian bridge in Miami also built a bridge in Virginia that\"}, {\"start\": 140.98, \"end\": 143.78, \"text\": \"partially collapsed.\"}, {\"start\": 143.78, \"end\": 149.38, \"text\": \"Here are images from that bridge collapsed.\"}, {\"start\": 149.39, \"end\": 161.75, \"text\": \"Figg Bridge Engineers was fined $28,000 after a 90 ton piece of the South Norfolk Jordan\"}, {\"start\": 161.75, \"end\": 170.46, \"text\": \"bridge fell and hurt four people in 2012.\"}, {\"start\": 170.46, \"end\": 181.3, \"text\": \"In a statement, Figg said \\\"We will fully cooperate with every appropriate authority in reviewing\"}, {\"start\": 181.3, \"end\": 182.7, \"text\": \"what happened and why.\"}, {\"start\": 182.7, \"end\": 189.78, \"text\": \"In our 40 year history, nothing like this has ever happened before.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 192.34, \"end\": 206.12, \"text\": \"In September of last year, 18-year-old Maxwell Gruver died after a hazing ritual at Phi Delta\"}, {\"start\": 206.12, \"end\": 217.92, \"text\": \"Theta fraternity at Louisiana State University.\"}, {\"start\": 217.92, \"end\": 231.46, \"text\": \"On Thursday a grand jury indicted these four men in connection with Gruver's death.\"}, {\"start\": 231.46, \"end\": 245.24, \"text\": \"An autopsy showed Gruver's blood alcohol content was .495%, more than six times the legal limit.\"}, {\"start\": 245.24, \"end\": 256.18, \"text\": \"The coroner says Gruver died of alcohol poisoning and aspiration, which means he suffocated\"}, {\"start\": 256.18, \"end\": 260.74, \"text\": \"on his own vomit.\"}, {\"start\": 260.74, \"end\": 269.22, \"text\": \"The Phi Delta Theta fraternity was kicked off LSU's campus after Gruver died.\"}, {\"start\": 269.22, \"end\": 279.2, \"text\": \"The grand jury charged one former fraternity member with negligent homicide and three others\"}, {\"start\": 279.2, \"end\": 282.84, \"text\": \"with hazing.\"}, {\"start\": 282.84, \"end\": 289.3, \"text\": \"Negligent homicide is a felony charge with a maximum sentence of five years in prison\"}, {\"start\": 289.3, \"end\": 293.68, \"text\": \"and a $5,000 fine.\"}, {\"start\": 293.68, \"end\": 300.76, \"text\": \"The maximum penalty for hazing is a $100 fine and 30 days in jail.\"}, {\"start\": 303.26, \"end\": 319.64, \"text\": \"Jennifer Lopez is sharing her experience of being sexually harassed in Hollywood.\"}, {\"start\": 319.64, \"end\": 326.97, \"text\": \"In an interview with \\\"Harper's Bazaar\\\" the actress, singer and producer detailed an experience\"}, {\"start\": 326.97, \"end\": 329.71, \"text\": \"she had very early in her career.\"}, {\"start\": 329.71, \"end\": 334.7, \"text\": \"She said the director of one of her first movies told her to take off her shirt and\"}, {\"start\": 334.7, \"end\": 336.26, \"text\": \"show her breasts.\"}, {\"start\": 336.26, \"end\": 339.74, \"text\": \"She says she was terrified but ultimately refused to remove her shirt.\"}, {\"start\": 339.74, \"end\": 346.34, \"text\": \"Lopez never revealed the director's name in the interview.\"}, {\"start\": 349.68, \"end\": 357.92, \"text\": \"If your boss catches you napping on the job or your teacher scolds you for falling asleep\"}, {\"start\": 357.92, \"end\": 362.24, \"text\": \"in class, just tell them you have a really good excuse.\"}, {\"start\": 362.24, \"end\": 366.18, \"text\": \"Today is \\\"World Sleep Day!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 366.18, \"end\": 374.16, \"text\": \"World Sleep Day was started in 2008 by the World Sleep Society and is designed to draw\"}, {\"start\": 374.16, \"end\": 379.92, \"text\": \"attention to the importance of and benefits associated with good, healthy sleep.\"}, {\"start\": 379.92, \"end\": 387.78, \"text\": \"According to several studies, sleep deprivation is a global epidemic that can lead to weight\"}, {\"start\": 387.78, \"end\": 404.86, \"text\": \"gain, mood swings, memory loss, depression and increase your risk of heart disease and stroke.\"}, {\"start\": 404.86, \"end\": 411.34, \"text\": \"It is also estimated sleep deprivation costs the US $400 billion in lost productivity on\"}, {\"start\": 411.34, \"end\": 413.62, \"text\": \"the job.\"}, {\"start\": 413.62, \"end\": 419.46, \"text\": \"So if you've got a few extra minutes today, go ahead and knockout for a few minutes.\"}, {\"start\": 419.46, \"end\": 425.6, \"text\": \"Better still, try to get a good 8 to 10 hours of sleep tonight.\"}, {\"start\": 428.58, \"end\": 440.08, \"text\": \"The Santa Barbara zoo welcomed the birth of a new giraffe calf -- and she came early.\"}, {\"start\": 440.14, \"end\": 443.52, \"text\": \"She wasn't expected until next month.\"}, {\"start\": 443.52, \"end\": 450.2, \"text\": \"But zoo staff say mom and baby are bonding and doing well.\"}, {\"start\": 450.2, \"end\": 455.64, \"text\": \"Now the zoo is hosting a public contest to name the calf.\"}, {\"start\": 455.64, \"end\": 470.16, \"text\": \"So far, the names inthe running are Amirah, Makena, Quinton and Nugget.\"}, {\"start\": 470.16, \"end\": 480.0, \"text\": \"A few miles away, the Los Angeles zoo debuted a new mob of meerkats.\"}, {\"start\": 480.0, \"end\": 486.78, \"text\": \"The zoo has been working with a breeding group and are hoping these meerkats will make more\"}, {\"start\": 486.78, \"end\": 488.7, \"text\": \"meerkats.\"}, {\"start\": 488.7, \"end\": 492.48, \"text\": \"The zoo is now home to three new females and for males.\"}, {\"start\": 492.48, \"end\": 498.2, \"text\": \"And according to the zoo, they are getting along with one another \\\"very well\\\"...\"}, {\"start\": 498.2, \"end\": 500.36, \"text\": \"...if you know what we mean.\"}, {\"start\": 503.52, \"end\": 506.42, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 506.42, \"end\": 508.23, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 508.23, \"end\": 510.46, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 510.46, \"end\": 514.6, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 514.6, \"end\": 520.66, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "UzbloJOxuaA": {
    "video_id": "UzbloJOxuaA",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.16.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171117",
    "duration": 637,
    "view_count": 202,
    "description": "November 16, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-HOUSE PASSES GOP TAX REFORM PLAN\n-SENATOR FRANKEN SEXUAL HARASSMENT ALLEGATIONS\n-MOORE YEARBOOK SIGNATURE COMPARISON \n-DRAKE THREATENS ALLEGED GROPER AT CONCERT\n-SCIENTISTS ISSUE DIRE WARNING TO HUMANITY\n-DEADLY FLOODING IN GREECE\n-POPE FRANCIS GETS NEW LAMBORGHINI\n-GIVING UP GIFTING\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 11.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 11.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.0, \"end\": 22.0, \"text\": \"House Republicans scored a major legislative victory today.\"}, {\"start\": 22.0, \"end\": 27.0, \"text\": \"They passed a massive tax overhaul. It's a much needed\"}, {\"start\": 27.0, \"end\": 32.0, \"text\": \"win for Republicans and President Trump but the\"}, {\"start\": 32.0, \"end\": 36.0, \"text\": \"victory might be short lived. On the Senate side there are\"}, {\"start\": 36.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"signs of trouble. Their version of a tax reform\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 46.0, \"text\": \"bill is still in the works, adding a repeal of the\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 50.0, \"text\": \"Obamacare individual mandate which supporters say brings\"}, {\"start\": 50.0, \"end\": 56.0, \"text\": \"a 338 billion dollar savings.\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 61.0, \"text\": \"Some Republicans are not 100 percent\"}, {\"start\": 61.0, \"end\": 63.0, \"text\": \"onboard with the new version.\"}, {\"start\": 63.0, \"end\": 66.0, \"text\": \"while others are on the fence. The president\"}, {\"start\": 67.0, \"end\": 72.0, \"text\": \"is optimistic, reportedly telling House members\"}, {\"start\": 72.0, \"end\": 75.0, \"text\": \"that the Senate will\"}, {\"start\": 75.024, \"end\": 77.024, \"text\": \"come around.\"}, {\"start\": 80.0, \"end\": 85.0, \"text\": \"Accusations of sexual harassment and assault are now being\"}, {\"start\": 85.0, \"end\": 90.0, \"text\": \"leveled at Senator Al Franken. His accuser\"}, {\"start\": 91.0, \"end\": 95.0, \"text\": \"shared this photo Thursday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 96.0, \"end\": 101.0, \"text\": \"The woman Leeann Tweeden, a morning\"}, {\"start\": 101.0, \"end\": 106.0, \"text\": \"news anchor on a talk radio show in Los\"}, {\"start\": 106.0, \"end\": 110.0, \"text\": \"Angeles, she said Franken, a comedian at the time,\"}, {\"start\": 111.0, \"end\": 116.0, \"text\": \"groped her and kissed her without her consent during a\"}, {\"start\": 116.0, \"end\": 121.0, \"text\": \"USO tour in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 122.0, \"end\": 128.0, \"text\": \"Tweeden says Franken wrote a skit\"}, {\"start\": 128.0, \"end\": 132.0, \"text\": \"which called for him to kiss her. She wrote that Franken\"}, {\"start\": 132.0, \"end\": 137.0, \"text\": \"repeatedly insisted they rehearse the kissing scene, even though\"}, {\"start\": 137.0, \"end\": 142.0, \"text\": \"she told him she didn't want to. She says she finally relented. She said\"}, {\"start\": 142.0, \"end\": 147.0, \"text\": \"Franken grabbed her head and stuck his tongue in her mouth.\"}, {\"start\": 147.0, \"end\": 152.0, \"text\": \"In a statement to reporters, Franken says he does not\"}, {\"start\": 152.0, \"end\": 157.0, \"text\": \"remember the skit rehearsal the same way but he said he sends\"}, {\"start\": 157.0, \"end\": 161.0, \"text\": \"his sincerest apologies to Leeann.\"}, {\"start\": 161.0, \"end\": 167.0, \"text\": \"Franken says the photo was intended to be funny but says he\"}, {\"start\": 168.0, \"end\": 174.0, \"text\": \"should not have done it. Senate Minority leader\"}, {\"start\": 174.0, \"end\": 178.0, \"text\": \"Chuch Schumer is calling for an\"}, {\"start\": 179.0, \"end\": 184.0, \"text\": \"ethics committee investigation into the allegations.\"}, {\"start\": 184.0, \"end\": 190.0, \"text\": \"Franken says he will cooperate fully.\"}, {\"start\": 193.0, \"end\": 198.0, \"text\": \"These signatures have now become the center of\"}, {\"start\": 198.0, \"end\": 204.0, \"text\": \"attention in the Roy Moore sexual assault story.\"}, {\"start\": 204.0, \"end\": 210.0, \"text\": \"Beverly Nelson has come forward and said the\"}, {\"start\": 210.0, \"end\": 215.0, \"text\": \"Alabama Senate candidate assaulted her when she\"}, {\"start\": 215.0, \"end\": 220.0, \"text\": \"was 16 years old. As proof that they knew each other back then\"}, {\"start\": 221.0, \"end\": 225.0, \"text\": \"Nelson and her attorney Gloria\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 230.0, \"text\": \"Allred presented a high school yearbook they\"}, {\"start\": 230.0, \"end\": 236.0, \"text\": \"said Moore signed in 1977.\"}, {\"start\": 236.0, \"end\": 241.0, \"text\": \"Moore's attorney cast doubt on that signature.\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 246.0, \"text\": \"He said he wants to examine the yearbook to see if it is\"}, {\"start\": 246.0, \"end\": 250.0, \"text\": \"really Moore's signature. Moore denies he pursued a sexual\"}, {\"start\": 250.0, \"end\": 255.0, \"text\": \"relationship with five teen girls while he was a district attorney in\"}, {\"start\": 255.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"his early 30s.\"}, {\"start\": 261.0, \"end\": 265.0, \"text\": \"And he is ignoring calls to step down from his Senate campaign.\"}, {\"start\": 268.0, \"end\": 273.0, \"text\": \"A word of warning -- this video contains some profanity but we have\"}, {\"start\": 273.0, \"end\": 278.0, \"text\": \"blanked out the words on the screen. On Tuesday rapper\"}, {\"start\": 278.0, \"end\": 282.0, \"text\": \"Drake interrupted his performance in Sydney Australia\"}, {\"start\": 283.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"after spotting a man apparently touching\"}, {\"start\": 288.0, \"end\": 294.0, \"text\": \"several women inappropriately.\"}, {\"start\": 294.0, \"end\": 298.0, \"text\": \"He pointed at the man and let him know it wasn't acceptable\"}, {\"start\": 299.0, \"end\": 306.0, \"text\": \"and he would not let it continue. Drake told his band\"}, {\"start\": 306.024, \"end\": 312.024, \"text\": \"to shut off the music and said this:\"}, {\"start\": 312.1, \"end\": 315.1, \"text\": \"Apparently the man did not stop.\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 323.0, \"text\": \"So Drake said this:\"}, {\"start\": 323.001, \"end\": 327.001, \"text\": \"Security eventually escorted the man from the building.\"}, {\"start\": 327.1, \"end\": 330.1, \"text\": \"Many Drake fans have praised him\"}, {\"start\": 331.0, \"end\": 334.0, \"text\": \"for taking a stand against sexual harassment.\"}, {\"start\": 338.024, \"end\": 339.999, \"text\": \"More than fifteen thousand scientists signed\"}, {\"start\": 341.0, \"end\": 345.0, \"text\": \"a letter to all of humanity and the message\"}, {\"start\": 345.024, \"end\": 350.024, \"text\": \"was not good.\"}, {\"start\": 351.0, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"It says that unless people change their habits\"}, {\"start\": 354.0, \"end\": 359.0, \"text\": \"Earth will become unable to sustain life in the manner we know.\"}, {\"start\": 359.0, \"end\": 365.0, \"text\": \"A similar letter was issued by the science community 25 years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 365.0, \"end\": 370.0, \"text\": \"This follow up letter notes that since that time the population has grown\"}, {\"start\": 370.0, \"end\": 375.0, \"text\": \"to 7.6 billion people. That's a 26 percent increase.\"}, {\"start\": 376.0, \"end\": 384.0, \"text\": \"And every mammal, reptile,\"}, {\"start\": 385.0, \"end\": 391.0, \"text\": \"amphibian\"}, {\"start\": 391.0, \"end\": 396.0, \"text\": \"and fish population declined\"}, {\"start\": 396.0, \"end\": 401.0, \"text\": \"by almost 30 percent during the same time. The letter also says\"}, {\"start\": 401.0, \"end\": 404.0, \"text\": \"the average global temperature has risen by over\"}, {\"start\": 405.0, \"end\": 409.0, \"text\": \"half a degree Celsius. And carbon dioxide\"}, {\"start\": 410.0, \"end\": 418.0, \"text\": \"emissions have increased\"}, {\"start\": 418.001, \"end\": 421.001, \"text\": \"by 62 percent.\"}, {\"start\": 421.1, \"end\": 425.1, \"text\": \"The only area where mankind has made progress\"}, {\"start\": 426.0, \"end\": 434.0, \"text\": \"is in shrinking the hole in the ozone layer.\"}, {\"start\": 435.0, \"end\": 441.0, \"text\": \"However, scientists say there is still time to reverse the damage.\"}, {\"start\": 444.024, \"end\": 447.024, \"text\": \"Flash floods triggered by heavy rain in\"}, {\"start\": 447.1, \"end\": 452.0, \"text\": \"Greece have killed at least 16 people.\"}, {\"start\": 452.0, \"end\": 456.0, \"text\": \"Twenty people have been injured\"}, {\"start\": 457.0, \"end\": 461.0, \"text\": \"and one person is missing. Parts of the national highway system\"}, {\"start\": 462.0, \"end\": 467.0, \"text\": \"have been destroyed and several roads\"}, {\"start\": 467.0, \"end\": 472.0, \"text\": \"are closed. Some people are trapped in\"}, {\"start\": 473.0, \"end\": 477.0, \"text\": \"their homes without power.\"}, {\"start\": 477.024, \"end\": 479.024, \"text\": \"The Greek prime minister has\"}, {\"start\": 479.048, \"end\": 487.048, \"text\": \"announced three days of mourning.\"}, {\"start\": 494.0, \"end\": 498.0, \"text\": \"Pope Francis\"}, {\"start\": 498.0, \"end\": 505.0, \"text\": \"just got a shiny new\"}, {\"start\": 505.0, \"end\": 511.0, \"text\": \"Lamborghini. The special edition Huracan\"}, {\"start\": 511.0, \"end\": 516.0, \"text\": \"was a gift but it's not meant\"}, {\"start\": 516.0, \"end\": 521.0, \"text\": \"for him to drive. The Vatican will\"}, {\"start\": 522.0, \"end\": 525.0, \"text\": \"auction off the vehicle to raise money\"}, {\"start\": 526.0, \"end\": 531.0, \"text\": \"for several charities.\"}, {\"start\": 531.0, \"end\": 534.0, \"text\": \"Pope Francis even signed\"}, {\"start\": 534.0, \"end\": 541.0, \"text\": \"the hood of the car hoping to raise the value.\"}, {\"start\": 544.024, \"end\": 546.099, \"text\": \"If you're dreading buying\"}, {\"start\": 546.1, \"end\": 551.1, \"text\": \"gifts this holiday season\"}, {\"start\": 552.0, \"end\": 557.0, \"text\": \"you are not alone. According to a new study\"}, {\"start\": 557.0, \"end\": 562.0, \"text\": \"most people want to stop giving gifts over\"}, {\"start\": 563.0, \"end\": 568.0, \"text\": \"the holiday season. Seventy percent of the people surveyed say\"}, {\"start\": 568.0, \"end\": 573.0, \"text\": \"that they would give up exchanging gifts if their family and friends\"}, {\"start\": 573.0, \"end\": 578.0, \"text\": \"agreed to do it. Forty-three percent say they feel pressured\"}, {\"start\": 579.0, \"end\": 584.0, \"text\": \"to spend money they don't have and 60 percent say they would\"}, {\"start\": 584.0, \"end\": 589.0, \"text\": \"rather just spend time with family and friends during the holidays.\"}, {\"start\": 589.0, \"end\": 593.0, \"text\": \"But if you do decide to shop, retail experts\"}, {\"start\": 593.0, \"end\": 598.0, \"text\": \"say the best thing to do is to set a budget,\"}, {\"start\": 598.0, \"end\": 603.0, \"text\": \"a limit as to how much you're going to spend and don't go over it.\"}, {\"start\": 603.024, \"end\": 606.024, \"text\": \"When you reach your spending limit, stop buying gifts.\"}, {\"start\": 609.025, \"end\": 611.025, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 611.1, \"end\": 615.1, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 616.0, \"end\": 621.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 621.0, \"end\": 628.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "Lwq1VFMR0Ig": {
    "video_id": "Lwq1VFMR0Ig",
    "title": "Sign1News celebrates deaf culture with local school (ASL - 3.31.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180401",
    "duration": 101,
    "view_count": 253,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.8, \"end\": 7.36, \"text\": \"We want to thank Cleveland Road elementary school for inviting us to participate in their\"}, {\"start\": 7.36, \"end\": 11.7, \"text\": \"Deaf Culture Celebration on Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 11.7, \"end\": 25.36, \"text\": \"Sign1News anchor Jethro Wooddall shared with the students his life story and what it's\"}, {\"start\": 25.36, \"end\": 31.44, \"text\": \"like to be a news anchor and a deaf interpreter.\"}, {\"start\": 31.44, \"end\": 38.02, \"text\": \"The kids was thoroughly engaged and asked lots of great questions.\"}, {\"start\": 38.02, \"end\": 44.68, \"text\": \"Afterwards all of the invited speakers fellowshipped in the cafeteria with the students.\"}, {\"start\": 44.68, \"end\": 50.24, \"text\": \"It was an exciting, inspiring and educational day for everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 50.24, \"end\": 56.52, \"text\": \"It was important for me to show the kids what they can achieve when they dream big, that\"}, {\"start\": 56.52, \"end\": 58.56, \"text\": \"nothing is impossible.\"}, {\"start\": 58.56, \"end\": 63.4, \"text\": \"If they thought being deaf would limited them, I'm here to prove them wrong and to show that\"}, {\"start\": 63.4, \"end\": 66.08, \"text\": \"they can become anything they want.\"}, {\"start\": 66.08, \"end\": 71.48, \"text\": \"This was such an important day for the students, teachers and staff.\"}, {\"start\": 71.48, \"end\": 75.62, \"text\": \"We all learned the different aspects of deaf culture but at the same time we learned that\"}, {\"start\": 75.62, \"end\": 80.34, \"text\": \"the deaf culture is not different than any other culture and should be honored equally.\"}, {\"start\": 80.34, \"end\": 82.48, \"text\": \"We learned so much!\"}, {\"start\": 82.48, \"end\": 89.2, \"text\": \"Now a lot of people know about deaf culture so it was cool having everyone come together\"}, {\"start\": 89.2, \"end\": 96.86, \"text\": \"to understand that being deaf is more than just a physical condition.\"}, {\"start\": 96.86, \"end\": 101.02, \"text\": \"It's about teaching hearing people who want to learn more about American Sign Language.\"}]"
  },
  "Ov97MJDKWPo": {
    "video_id": "Ov97MJDKWPo",
    "title": "Don't fall for these April Fool's Day jokes (ASL - 4.1.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180402",
    "duration": 140,
    "view_count": 640,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.42, \"end\": 6.52, \"text\": \"It is not only Easter, is also April Fools' Day.\"}, {\"start\": 6.52, \"end\": 13.0, \"text\": \"And this year a few corporations got in on the April Fools' Day pranking.\"}, {\"start\": 13.1, \"end\": 21.74, \"text\": \"So be careful and don't fall for these fake commercials.\"}, {\"start\": 21.74, \"end\": 29.58, \"text\": \"Burger King posted a video announcing the Chocolate Whopper, which has a chocolate cake\"}, {\"start\": 29.58, \"end\": 42.64, \"text\": \"bun, raspberry syrup instead of ketchup and white chocolate rings instead of onions.\"}, {\"start\": 42.66, \"end\": 50.72, \"text\": \"Auntie Anne's pretzels sent out a press release for \\\"Heavenly Scent\\\" essential pretzel oils.\"}, {\"start\": 50.72, \"end\": 59.8, \"text\": \"It says you can smell like a freshly baked, salty or cinnamon twist pretzel.\"}, {\"start\": 59.94, \"end\": 69.4, \"text\": \"But a line at the bottom of the press release revealed it as fake news.\"}, {\"start\": 69.4, \"end\": 74.84, \"text\": \"The company says: \\\"We recommend consuming pretzels, not rubbing them on your skin and\"}, {\"start\": 74.84, \"end\": 79.48, \"text\": \"hair as a substitute.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 79.48, \"end\": 87.02, \"text\": \"Pindrop, a phone and voice communication security company, released this ad for \\\"tongue printing\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 87.02, \"end\": 88.72, \"text\": \"technology.\"}, {\"start\": 88.76, \"end\": 92.74, \"text\": \"It's top knot security.\"}, {\"start\": 92.74, \"end\": 98.98, \"text\": \"Just lick your phone and you're logged in.\"}, {\"start\": 99.06, \"end\": 106.8, \"text\": \"T-Mobile went all out this year, introducing the world's first smart shoe phone called the\"}, {\"start\": 106.8, \"end\": 110.48, \"text\": \"T-Mobile Sidekicks.\"}, {\"start\": 110.6, \"end\": 119.16, \"text\": \"The soles of the shoes turn into speakers, the shoe laces are retractable earbuds and\"}, {\"start\": 119.16, \"end\": 123.28, \"text\": \"there's a camera in the toe.\"}, {\"start\": 123.28, \"end\": 131.6, \"text\": \"The smartphone technology is not real, but if you want the actual pink footwear you can\"}, {\"start\": 131.68, \"end\": 138.88, \"text\": \"preorder them at Bemagenta.com before April 15.\"}]"
  },
  "Q3uGuYnV4Mc": {
    "video_id": "Q3uGuYnV4Mc",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.30.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180131",
    "duration": 513,
    "view_count": 1111,
    "description": "1.30.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-\"Glee\" actor Mark Salling dies\n-Lawmakers will wear black to State of the Union Address\n-Secret Service says beware of ATM \"jackpotting\"\n-Uber wants drivers to help fight sex trafficking\n-Amazon unveils \"Spheres\" workspace for employees\n-Scientists grow new ears for kids with defects \n-Healthy fast food options\n-Snow fall in the desert!\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, par",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.76, \"end\": 8.94, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.94, \"end\": 11.26, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.26, \"end\": 12.94, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.94, \"end\": 15.96, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.8, \"end\": 26.44, \"text\": \"According to his attorney, former \\\"Glee\\\" actor Mark Salling has died.\"}, {\"start\": 26.44, \"end\": 29.2, \"text\": \"He was 35 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 29.2, \"end\": 36.1, \"text\": \"TMZ and E! network both say Salling committed suicide.\"}, {\"start\": 36.14, \"end\": 43.32, \"text\": \"Police tell CNN they were called to a wooded area around 8:50 Tuesday morning to investigate\"}, {\"start\": 43.32, \"end\": 44.96, \"text\": \"a death.\"}, {\"start\": 44.96, \"end\": 57.6, \"text\": \"Salling was indicted in May 2016 on charges of receiving and possessing child pornography.\"}, {\"start\": 57.6, \"end\": 70.68, \"text\": \"He pleaded guilty to one count of possession of child pornography and was scheduled to\"}, {\"start\": 70.68, \"end\": 72.74, \"text\": \"be sentenced on March 7.\"}, {\"start\": 72.74, \"end\": 81.46, \"text\": \"According to the plea agreement, he would've been sent to federal prison for 4 to 7 years.\"}, {\"start\": 84.14, \"end\": 92.86, \"text\": \"Several members of Congress are planning to make statements during President Trump's first\"}, {\"start\": 92.86, \"end\": 95.8, \"text\": \"State of the Union address Tuesday night.\"}, {\"start\": 95.8, \"end\": 109.54, \"text\": \"At least eight members of Congress plan to bring sexual assault survivors or activists\"}, {\"start\": 109.54, \"end\": 111.2, \"text\": \"as their guests.\"}, {\"start\": 111.2, \"end\": 117.54, \"text\": \"Many say the #METOO movement has inspired them to invite their guests.\"}, {\"start\": 117.54, \"end\": 124.68, \"text\": \"And several female Democratic lawmakers also plan to wear black Tuesday night to show support\"}, {\"start\": 124.74, \"end\": 130.2, \"text\": \"for movements protesting sexual harassment and assault.\"}, {\"start\": 130.2, \"end\": 136.62, \"text\": \"The president himself continues to be confronted by accusations, ranging from sexual harassment\"}, {\"start\": 136.62, \"end\": 141.64, \"text\": \"and sexual assault to lewd behavior, from at least 15 women.\"}, {\"start\": 143.62, \"end\": 151.7, \"text\": \"Banks in the US are being warned about a new hacking scheme.\"}, {\"start\": 151.7, \"end\": 160.58, \"text\": \"It's called \\\"jackpotting\\\" and it involves stealing money from ATMs.\"}, {\"start\": 160.66, \"end\": 172.26, \"text\": \"Authorities say robbers are using malware and hacking tools to get control of cash machines.\"}, {\"start\": 172.26, \"end\": 175.78, \"text\": \"Once it's done, the machine dispenses the cash inside quickly, as if the robber had just\"}, {\"start\": 175.78, \"end\": 177.44, \"text\": \"won a jackpot.\"}, {\"start\": 177.56, \"end\": 186.12, \"text\": \"Secret Service officials say stand-alone machines, like the ones in retailers and pharmacies,\"}, {\"start\": 186.12, \"end\": 188.84, \"text\": \"are especially vulnerable.\"}, {\"start\": 188.84, \"end\": 195.24, \"text\": \"Jackpotting has been reported in Asia and Europe, but it's a relatively new threat in\"}, {\"start\": 195.32, \"end\": 199.48, \"text\": \"the United States.\"}, {\"start\": 199.48, \"end\": 207.04, \"text\": \"At least six of this type of theft have happened within the last few days with more than one\"}, {\"start\": 207.2, \"end\": 209.72, \"text\": \"million dollars stolen.\"}, {\"start\": 211.76, \"end\": 223.0, \"text\": \"Uber has partnered with several organizations to raise awareness about human sex trafficking\"}, {\"start\": 223.0, \"end\": 230.32, \"text\": \"and calls its drivers \\\"everyday heros\\\" for their unique position to help.\"}, {\"start\": 230.32, \"end\": 236.36, \"text\": \"In a news release on Monday, Uber said its new efforts will make it easier for drivers\"}, {\"start\": 236.36, \"end\": 244.04, \"text\": \"to report suspicious behavior to the national human trafficking hotline.\"}, {\"start\": 244.04, \"end\": 252.72, \"text\": \"Uber said in December 2016, an observant Sacramento-\"}, {\"start\": 252.72, \"end\": 259.32, \"text\": \"area driver helped a 16-year-old girl escape from a human trafficking operation.\"}, {\"start\": 259.4, \"end\": 270.0, \"text\": \"The international labor organization estimated there were more than 40 million adults and\"}, {\"start\": 270.0, \"end\": 273.72, \"text\": \"children affected worldwide in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 273.72, \"end\": 283.0, \"text\": \"If you or someone you know is a victim, call the National Human Trafficking Resource Center\"}, {\"start\": 283.0, \"end\": 287.92, \"text\": \"at 1-888-373-7888.\"}, {\"start\": 289.24, \"end\": 301.16, \"text\": \"Amazon just opened three new buildings in Seattle in the shape of spheres.\"}, {\"start\": 301.16, \"end\": 307.48, \"text\": \"The company hopes it will become a new kind of workspace for its employees.\"}, {\"start\": 307.56, \"end\": 317.72, \"text\": \"There are treehouse meeting spaces and waterfalls so employees feel like they're working in\"}, {\"start\": 317.72, \"end\": 319.8, \"text\": \"a tropical rain forest.\"}, {\"start\": 319.8, \"end\": 330.64, \"text\": \"There are more than 40,000 plants, including a 55-foot ficus tree named \\\"Rubi.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 330.72, \"end\": 340.52, \"text\": \"Amazon hopes the sphere workspace will inspire the next big idea in the corporate world.\"}, {\"start\": 342.36, \"end\": 351.92, \"text\": \"According to a study published in the journal \\\"E-Bio-Medicine\\\" scientists in China have\"}, {\"start\": 352.04, \"end\": 366.4, \"text\": \"used 3-D printing and cell culturing to grow new ears for children born with defects.\"}, {\"start\": 366.4, \"end\": 369.6, \"text\": \"It's a first-of-its-kind study.\"}, {\"start\": 369.6, \"end\": 379.3, \"text\": \"In the study, researchers collected cartilage cells from the children's ears.\"}, {\"start\": 379.3, \"end\": 384.84, \"text\": \"They use those cells to grow new, ear-shaped cartilage based on 3-D printed models of the\"}, {\"start\": 384.84, \"end\": 386.84, \"text\": \"children's healthy ears.\"}, {\"start\": 386.84, \"end\": 391.2, \"text\": \"The next step is to transfer the newly engineered ears to the children and perform ear reconstruction.\"}, {\"start\": 391.2, \"end\": 396.84, \"text\": \"The process will require more research before it's widely available to patients in a clinical\"}, {\"start\": 396.84, \"end\": 399.16, \"text\": \"setting.\"}, {\"start\": 400.6, \"end\": 406.6, \"text\": \"Sometimes when we are in a hurry, eating fast food is the only option.\"}, {\"start\": 406.68, \"end\": 412.56, \"text\": \"But you can still be healthy even if you grab something from the drive-through.\"}, {\"start\": 412.64, \"end\": 415.32, \"text\": \"Here are a few tips to help you make healthier fast food choices.\"}, {\"start\": 415.32, \"end\": 417.16, \"text\": \"Think veggies first.\"}, {\"start\": 417.16, \"end\": 420.88, \"text\": \"You want half of your plate to be vegetables.\"}, {\"start\": 420.88, \"end\": 430.96, \"text\": \"If you get a salad, avoid fried toppings and over-sized portions of cheese.\"}, {\"start\": 431.04, \"end\": 435.64, \"text\": \"Don't go overboard on the salad dressing.\"}, {\"start\": 435.64, \"end\": 439.04, \"text\": \"One or 2 tablespoons is enough.\"}, {\"start\": 439.04, \"end\": 447.8, \"text\": \"And oil-based salad dressings are better than the cream-based ones.\"}, {\"start\": 447.8, \"end\": 453.2, \"text\": \"Also skip the fries and don't order a soda with your meal.\"}, {\"start\": 454.88, \"end\": 458.12, \"text\": \"Take a look at this.\"}, {\"start\": 458.12, \"end\": 461.32, \"text\": \"That is snow in the desert!\"}, {\"start\": 461.32, \"end\": 467.2, \"text\": \"For the past two days several regions of Morocco have experienced snowfall.\"}, {\"start\": 467.2, \"end\": 471.12, \"text\": \"It's not unusual to see snow in the northern mountainous parts of Morocco, but this snow\"}, {\"start\": 471.12, \"end\": 475.12, \"text\": \"fell in the southern region, a very rare occurrence.\"}, {\"start\": 475.12, \"end\": 480.68, \"text\": \"Residents say this is the first time they've witnessed snowfall in the desert in more than\"}, {\"start\": 480.76, \"end\": 483.12, \"text\": \"50 years.\"}, {\"start\": 485.44, \"end\": 488.32, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 488.48, \"end\": 489.88, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 489.88, \"end\": 492.56, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 492.56, \"end\": 497.72, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 497.88, \"end\": 504.4, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "xRATfMBbnoY": {
    "video_id": "xRATfMBbnoY",
    "title": "Fans to decide which M&M flavor will stay (ASL - 3.8.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180308",
    "duration": 51,
    "view_count": 307,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.58, \"end\": 9.26, \"text\": \"On Wednesday the candy company M&amp;Ms announced that it was introducing three new flavors.\"}, {\"start\": 9.26, \"end\": 14.06, \"text\": \"But only one flavor will stay on the shelves.\"}, {\"start\": 14.06, \"end\": 29.7, \"text\": \"Crunchy Espresso, Crunchy Raspberry and Crunchy Mint will be a part of a flavor vote campaign.\"}, {\"start\": 29.7, \"end\": 34.54, \"text\": \"People who try the candies can vote on whether they like snacking on chocolates that taste\"}, {\"start\": 34.54, \"end\": 42.84, \"text\": \"like a morning cup of coffee, something tart or something minty fresh.\"}, {\"start\": 42.84, \"end\": 49.76, \"text\": \"Fans can cast their vote by text or on social media.\"}]"
  },
  "UihV32x1iQk": {
    "video_id": "UihV32x1iQk",
    "title": "October 5, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171006",
    "duration": 553,
    "view_count": 349,
    "description": "October 5, 2017\nNews for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).\n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-VEGAS SHOOTING NEW DETAILS\n-UNLV SPECIAL HELMETS\n-PRIVATE FLIGHTS BRING SUPPLIES TO PUERTO RICO\n-TROPICAL STORM NATE\n-WORST CHOLERA OUTBREAK IN MODERN HISTORY\n-NETFLIX RAISING PRICES\n-NEW GOOGLE GADGETS\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN, FOX, ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 11.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.0, \"end\": 16.0, \"text\": \"I am Candace Jones. And here are your top\"}, {\"start\": 16.0, \"end\": 18.0, \"text\": \"stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 22.0, \"end\": 26.0, \"text\": \"In Nevada and around the country investigators are still looking\"}, {\"start\": 26.0, \"end\": 31.0, \"text\": \"for a motive behind Sunday's deadly shooting in\"}, {\"start\": 31.0, \"end\": 36.0, \"text\": \"Las Vegas.\"}, {\"start\": 36.0, \"end\": 40.0, \"text\": \"Police say the shooter Stephen\"}, {\"start\": 40.0, \"end\": 46.0, \"text\": \"Paddock had a secret life.\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 49.0, \"text\": \"He spent decades collecting\"}, {\"start\": 50.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"weapons and\"}, {\"start\": 55.0, \"end\": 61.0, \"text\": \"ammunition.\"}, {\"start\": 61.0, \"end\": 65.0, \"text\": \"Investigators say there is an indication that\"}, {\"start\": 65.0, \"end\": 70.0, \"text\": \"Paddock had planned to escape but instead left a\"}, {\"start\": 70.0, \"end\": 77.0, \"text\": \"suicide note and then killed himself.\"}, {\"start\": 77.0, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"Authorities also suspect Paddock\"}, {\"start\": 83.0, \"end\": 90.0, \"text\": \"may have had an accomplice.\"}, {\"start\": 90.1, \"end\": 93.1, \"text\": \"And now they are pleading with the public for help\"}, {\"start\": 94.0, \"end\": 100.0, \"text\": \"in finding him or her. Police say Paddock's\"}, {\"start\": 101.0, \"end\": 105.0, \"text\": \"girlfriend Marilou Danley\"}, {\"start\": 105.0, \"end\": 112.0, \"text\": \"is not a suspect.\"}, {\"start\": 113.0, \"end\": 118.0, \"text\": \"The University of Nevada-Las Vegas'\"}, {\"start\": 118.0, \"end\": 122.0, \"text\": \"football team will not wear their usual helmets\"}, {\"start\": 122.0, \"end\": 126.0, \"text\": \"when they play Saturday. Instead\"}, {\"start\": 126.0, \"end\": 130.0, \"text\": \"they will wear a special black helmet. The\"}, {\"start\": 130.0, \"end\": 137.0, \"text\": \"helmets will honor the victims of the Las Vegas shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 137.0, \"end\": 143.0, \"text\": \"The decal is a red ribbon with Las Vegas printed on it.\"}, {\"start\": 143.0, \"end\": 148.0, \"text\": \"All of UNLV's sports teams will wear the ribbon\"}, {\"start\": 148.0, \"end\": 155.0, \"text\": \"on their uniforms this season.\"}, {\"start\": 155.1, \"end\": 159.1, \"text\": \"The team will also hand out stickers\"}, {\"start\": 159.1, \"end\": 164.1, \"text\": \"of the ribbon to fans.\"}, {\"start\": 166.0, \"end\": 171.0, \"text\": \"Two weeks after Hurricane Maria struck Puerto Rico\"}, {\"start\": 171.0, \"end\": 176.0, \"text\": \"most residents are still without food, water and power.\"}, {\"start\": 176.0, \"end\": 180.0, \"text\": \"People have stepped up to deliver supplies to the island\"}, {\"start\": 181.0, \"end\": 186.0, \"text\": \"and help evacuate people. But\"}, {\"start\": 186.0, \"end\": 194.0, \"text\": \"these people are not working for the U.S. government.\"}, {\"start\": 194.0, \"end\": 197.0, \"text\": \"They are all volunteers and they say their mission is\"}, {\"start\": 197.0, \"end\": 199.0, \"text\": \"to save lives. One group says\"}, {\"start\": 201.0, \"end\": 206.0, \"text\": \"filmmaker Tyler Perry donated many\"}, {\"start\": 206.0, \"end\": 210.0, \"text\": \"supplies and an airplane.\"}, {\"start\": 211.0, \"end\": 215.0, \"text\": \"Volunteers say the plane will bring tons of supplies\"}, {\"start\": 215.0, \"end\": 221.0, \"text\": \"to the island.\"}, {\"start\": 221.0, \"end\": 226.0, \"text\": \"And on the way back the plane will be empty. So volunteers can\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 230.0, \"text\": \"evacuate people off the island. When the plane is empty\"}, {\"start\": 230.0, \"end\": 238.0, \"text\": \"they will load up more supplies and do\"}, {\"start\": 238.024, \"end\": 241.024, \"text\": \"do it all over again.\"}, {\"start\": 245.0, \"end\": 248.0, \"text\": \"Today tropical storm Nate\"}, {\"start\": 249.0, \"end\": 257.0, \"text\": \"is expected to move inland over Honduras.\"}, {\"start\": 258.0, \"end\": 262.0, \"text\": \"Right now heavy rain is causing flash\"}, {\"start\": 263.0, \"end\": 267.0, \"text\": \"flooding and mudslides.\"}, {\"start\": 268.0, \"end\": 272.0, \"text\": \"By early Friday the center of the storm will move\"}, {\"start\": 272.0, \"end\": 280.0, \"text\": \"back into the Caribbean and likely intensify.\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"And over the weekend the storm will likely intensify\"}, {\"start\": 287.1, \"end\": 290.7, \"text\": \"again as it moves into the warm\"}, {\"start\": 290.7, \"end\": 293.7, \"text\": \"waters of the Gulf of Mexico.\"}, {\"start\": 295.0, \"end\": 300.0, \"text\": \"In Yemen the country is experiencing\"}, {\"start\": 303.0, \"end\": 310.0, \"text\": \"an unprecedented outbreak of cholera.\"}, {\"start\": 310.0, \"end\": 314.0, \"text\": \"The World Health Organization says it is the\"}, {\"start\": 314.0, \"end\": 317.0, \"text\": \"worst outbreak in modern history and is expected to\"}, {\"start\": 317.0, \"end\": 325.0, \"text\": \"get worse. The symptoms are diarrhea,\"}, {\"start\": 325.0, \"end\": 332.0, \"text\": \"nausea, vomiting and dehydration.\"}, {\"start\": 332.0, \"end\": 335.0, \"text\": \"It can also lead to shock, seizures\"}, {\"start\": 335.0, \"end\": 341.0, \"text\": \"and a coma for weeks, months, even years.\"}, {\"start\": 341.1, \"end\": 346.1, \"text\": \"Right now there are 750,000 people\"}, {\"start\": 346.1, \"end\": 351.1, \"text\": \"across the country with cholera. And those numbers are\"}, {\"start\": 351.1, \"end\": 356.1, \"text\": \"expected to rise. Because the\"}, {\"start\": 356.1, \"end\": 362.1, \"text\": \"country has been at war for the past two years\"}, {\"start\": 362.1, \"end\": 366.1, \"text\": \"there are only a few hospitals available to\"}, {\"start\": 366.1, \"end\": 370.1, \"text\": \"treat patients.\"}, {\"start\": 370.1, \"end\": 374.1, \"text\": \"People are eating expired food or food that has been\"}, {\"start\": 374.1, \"end\": 379.1, \"text\": \"contaminated because they don't have a choice.\"}, {\"start\": 379.1, \"end\": 382.1, \"text\": \"And the drinking water is contaminated with water\"}, {\"start\": 382.1, \"end\": 384.1, \"text\": \"from the sewage.\"}, {\"start\": 391.0, \"end\": 396.0, \"text\": \"For 2 years Netflix has not\"}, {\"start\": 396.001, \"end\": 399.901, \"text\": \"raised prices.\"}, {\"start\": 400.0, \"end\": 404.0, \"text\": \"According to USA Today\"}, {\"start\": 404.0, \"end\": 407.0, \"text\": \"Netflix's most popular\"}, {\"start\": 407.0, \"end\": 410.0, \"text\": \"plan will now cost\"}, {\"start\": 410.0, \"end\": 417.0, \"text\": \"$10.99 a month. That's a $1 increase.\"}, {\"start\": 417.1, \"end\": 424.1, \"text\": \"The premium plan will go up by $2 every month\"}, {\"start\": 424.1, \"end\": 430.1, \"text\": \"to $13.99 a month.\"}, {\"start\": 430.1, \"end\": 438.1, \"text\": \"The basic plan will remain\"}, {\"start\": 438.1, \"end\": 441.1, \"text\": \"unchanged at $7.99 a month.\"}, {\"start\": 441.1, \"end\": 447.1, \"text\": \"The new prices will be phased in over several months.\"}, {\"start\": 447.1, \"end\": 452.1, \"text\": \"The price increase will begin for current\"}, {\"start\": 452.1, \"end\": 460.1, \"text\": \"subscribers on October 19th.\"}, {\"start\": 464.0, \"end\": 468.0, \"text\": \"This month Google has new gadgets coming out.\"}, {\"start\": 468.1, \"end\": 476.1, \"text\": \"There is the new Pixel 2 and Pixel 2XL.\"}, {\"start\": 476.1, \"end\": 479.1, \"text\": \"The phones are water\"}, {\"start\": 479.1, \"end\": 483.1, \"text\": \"resistant. They have a powerful rear camera\"}, {\"start\": 483.1, \"end\": 488.1, \"text\": \"and fingerprint sensors. If\"}, {\"start\": 488.1, \"end\": 493.1, \"text\": \"you point the phone camera on something like a sign\"}, {\"start\": 493.1, \"end\": 498.1, \"text\": \"or an animal the lens will give you information like phone\"}, {\"start\": 498.1, \"end\": 502.1, \"text\": \"numbers or a dog's breed.\"}, {\"start\": 504.0, \"end\": 509.0, \"text\": \"The pixel does not have a headphone jack. Instead it\"}, {\"start\": 509.0, \"end\": 517.0, \"text\": \"has pixel wireless headphones.\"}, {\"start\": 518.0, \"end\": 522.0, \"text\": \"The buds are connected to a string\"}, {\"start\": 523.0, \"end\": 524.0, \"text\": \"but not on the phone.\"}, {\"start\": 524.0, \"end\": 529.0, \"text\": \"It is wireless.\"}, {\"start\": 532.0, \"end\": 536.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for the day. I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 537.0, \"end\": 544.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Your life.Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "9F3Q_LctJFw": {
    "video_id": "9F3Q_LctJFw",
    "title": "Curious penguins find camera, take selfie video (ASL - 3.9.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180309",
    "duration": 75,
    "view_count": 358,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.6, \"end\": 16.16, \"text\": \"Two emperor penguins in Antarctica stumbled across a camera left in the ice by an expeditioner.\"}, {\"start\": 16.16, \"end\": 21.12, \"text\": \"The curious birds flipped it over to face skyward and then took a selfie video!\"}, {\"start\": 21.12, \"end\": 30.08, \"text\": \"The Australian Antarctic division posted this 38 second clip on its Twitter page.\"}, {\"start\": 30.08, \"end\": 32.0, \"text\": \"Here it is.\"}, {\"start\": 65.28, \"end\": 74.08, \"text\": \"The cute clip already has over 200,000 views and that number is going up!\"}]"
  },
  "xADNh5Mu_7g": {
    "video_id": "xADNh5Mu_7g",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.18.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171019",
    "duration": 492,
    "view_count": 210,
    "description": "October 18, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-JEFF SESSIONS GRILLED ON CAPITOL HILL\n-CALIFORNIA FIREFIGHTERS GAIN UPPER HAND\n-PUERTO RICO WATER CRISIS\n-JAY-Z'S COMPANY HOLDS DISASTER RELIEF CONCERT\n-NFL OWNERS DISCUSS FLAG PROTEST\n-NFL STAR DONATES SALARY TO CHARITIES\n-KANGAROO FIGHT CLUB\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organiza",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"And here are our top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.0, \"end\": 23.0, \"text\": \"Today on Capitol Hill Attorney General\"}, {\"start\": 23.0, \"end\": 28.0, \"text\": \"Jeff Sessions was\"}, {\"start\": 28.0, \"end\": 32.0, \"text\": \"grilled by his former colleagues.\"}, {\"start\": 33.0, \"end\": 37.0, \"text\": \"The Senate judiciary hearing covered a range of topics\"}, {\"start\": 37.0, \"end\": 42.0, \"text\": \"including Russia's ties to the\"}, {\"start\": 42.0, \"end\": 46.0, \"text\": \"presidential election and if Sessions\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 51.0, \"text\": \"had conversations with President Trump\"}, {\"start\": 52.0, \"end\": 56.0, \"text\": \"regarding Russia.\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 60.0, \"text\": \"Sessions refused to answer questions about confidential\"}, {\"start\": 60.0, \"end\": 66.0, \"text\": \"conversations with President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 67.0, \"end\": 72.0, \"text\": \"If you recall, during Sessions'\"}, {\"start\": 73.0, \"end\": 78.0, \"text\": \"confirmation hearings, he failed to disclose\"}, {\"start\": 78.0, \"end\": 83.0, \"text\": \"that he had met with the Russian ambassador during the 2016\"}, {\"start\": 83.0, \"end\": 88.0, \"text\": \"election. The fallout from that eventually led\"}, {\"start\": 88.0, \"end\": 92.0, \"text\": \"to Sessions recusing himself from the Russian investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 95.0, \"end\": 100.0, \"text\": \"We have some good news from Northern California.\"}, {\"start\": 100.0, \"end\": 105.0, \"text\": \"The two largest fires are now 60 percent contained.\"}, {\"start\": 105.0, \"end\": 110.0, \"text\": \"The winds are dying down and rain is in the\"}, {\"start\": 110.0, \"end\": 115.0, \"text\": \"forecast for later this week. But there is still lots of\"}, {\"start\": 115.0, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"damage to deal with. The flames have already\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 125.0, \"text\": \"caused an estimated\"}, {\"start\": 125.0, \"end\": 130.0, \"text\": \"three billion dollars in\"}, {\"start\": 130.0, \"end\": 136.0, \"text\": \"damage. And 88 people are still missing.\"}, {\"start\": 136.0, \"end\": 141.0, \"text\": \"People returning to their homes are realizing they have lost\"}, {\"start\": 141.0, \"end\": 147.0, \"text\": \"everything and have to start all over again.\"}, {\"start\": 147.0, \"end\": 151.0, \"text\": \"Officials say it could take years to\"}, {\"start\": 151.0, \"end\": 159.0, \"text\": \"build back their community.\"}, {\"start\": 162.0, \"end\": 166.0, \"text\": \"It's been nearly a month since Hurricane Maria\"}, {\"start\": 166.0, \"end\": 171.0, \"text\": \"devastated Puerto Rico. Many residents are still desperate to\"}, {\"start\": 171.0, \"end\": 175.0, \"text\": \"obtain the basic necessities like healthy drinking\"}, {\"start\": 175.0, \"end\": 180.0, \"text\": \"water. People are so desperate that\"}, {\"start\": 180.0, \"end\": 186.0, \"text\": \"they are drinking contaminated water.\"}, {\"start\": 186.0, \"end\": 191.0, \"text\": \"Some water faucets have police officers guarding them,\"}, {\"start\": 192.0, \"end\": 197.0, \"text\": \"chain link fences and signs that say \\\"Danger.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 197.0, \"end\": 201.0, \"text\": \"People are ignoring all of that just to get something to drink.\"}, {\"start\": 201.0, \"end\": 206.0, \"text\": \"Now the Environmental\"}, {\"start\": 207.0, \"end\": 212.0, \"text\": \"Protection Agency is\"}, {\"start\": 212.0, \"end\": 218.0, \"text\": \"concerned that Puerto Rico could be hit with widespread diseases\"}, {\"start\": 218.0, \"end\": 222.0, \"text\": \"and illnesses caused by drinking contaminated water.\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 229.0, \"text\": \"Last night rapper\"}, {\"start\": 229.0, \"end\": 235.0, \"text\": \"Jay-Z brought in some of the biggest names in the music industry\"}, {\"start\": 235.0, \"end\": 239.0, \"text\": \"to raise money for\"}, {\"start\": 239.0, \"end\": 245.0, \"text\": \"hurricane and earthquake victims.\"}, {\"start\": 246.0, \"end\": 253.0, \"text\": \"The event was called Tidal X Brooklyn.\"}, {\"start\": 255.0, \"end\": 259.0, \"text\": \"The goal was to provide aide to communities\"}, {\"start\": 259.0, \"end\": 263.0, \"text\": \"devastated by Hurricanes Harvey, Irma and Maria\"}, {\"start\": 263.0, \"end\": 271.0, \"text\": \"as well as victims of the massive earthquakes in Mexico.\"}, {\"start\": 272.0, \"end\": 276.0, \"text\": \"Proceeds from ticket sales will go to various relief\"}, {\"start\": 276.0, \"end\": 282.0, \"text\": \"and recovery organizations.\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 289.0, \"text\": \"Today in New York NFL Commissioner\"}, {\"start\": 289.0, \"end\": 294.0, \"text\": \"Roger Goodell met with team owners\"}, {\"start\": 294.0, \"end\": 298.0, \"text\": \"for a 2-day session. They were there to discuss\"}, {\"start\": 298.0, \"end\": 303.0, \"text\": \"the protest some players have made against\"}, {\"start\": 303.0, \"end\": 308.0, \"text\": \"the national anthem. Goodell says he believes\"}, {\"start\": 308.0, \"end\": 314.0, \"text\": \"players who kneel during the national anthem are not trying to disrespect the flag.\"}, {\"start\": 314.0, \"end\": 319.0, \"text\": \"However the league still\"}, {\"start\": 319.0, \"end\": 326.0, \"text\": \"believes they should stand.\"}, {\"start\": 327.0, \"end\": 329.0, \"text\": \"He said that there would be no change\"}, {\"start\": 329.0, \"end\": 335.0, \"text\": \"in the NFL's policy which states that players should stand for the national anthem.\"}, {\"start\": 335.0, \"end\": 342.0, \"text\": \"But they are not required to do so.\"}, {\"start\": 346.0, \"end\": 348.0, \"text\": \"NFL star\"}, {\"start\": 348.0, \"end\": 353.0, \"text\": \"Chris Long has decided to give all of the\"}, {\"start\": 354.0, \"end\": 360.0, \"text\": \"money he earned this season to different charities.\"}, {\"start\": 361.0, \"end\": 364.0, \"text\": \"He has already given his first six paychecks to\"}, {\"start\": 364.0, \"end\": 370.0, \"text\": \"two charities in his hometown\"}, {\"start\": 371.0, \"end\": 375.0, \"text\": \"Charlottesville, Virginia.\"}, {\"start\": 375.0, \"end\": 379.0, \"text\": \"He says he will give the other 10 checks\"}, {\"start\": 379.0, \"end\": 385.0, \"text\": \"to charities in\"}, {\"start\": 385.0, \"end\": 389.0, \"text\": \"Philadelphia, Boston and St. Louis.\"}, {\"start\": 389.0, \"end\": 394.0, \"text\": \"The goal of all of these charities is equality in education. Long wants\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 399.0, \"text\": \"to make education easily accessible for underserved children but also help\"}, {\"start\": 399.0, \"end\": 404.0, \"text\": \"them develop strong social and emotional character.\"}, {\"start\": 404.0, \"end\": 408.0, \"text\": \"Long is encouraging fans and businesses\"}, {\"start\": 408.0, \"end\": 412.0, \"text\": \"to join his campaign.\"}, {\"start\": 415.0, \"end\": 420.0, \"text\": \"Check out this video!\"}, {\"start\": 420.0, \"end\": 424.0, \"text\": \"In Australia, police helicopters\"}, {\"start\": 425.0, \"end\": 429.0, \"text\": \"capture amazing nighttime video of kangaroos fight.\"}, {\"start\": 429.0, \"end\": 434.0, \"text\": \"The fight was captured in the middle of\"}, {\"start\": 434.0, \"end\": 441.0, \"text\": \"the night by infrared camera.\"}, {\"start\": 441.1, \"end\": 444.0, \"text\": \"The two kangaroos used their\"}, {\"start\": 444.0, \"end\": 449.0, \"text\": \"arms and legs to combat one another.\"}, {\"start\": 449.0, \"end\": 453.0, \"text\": \"A third kangaroo can be seen in the background.\"}, {\"start\": 455.0, \"end\": 458.0, \"text\": \"Kangaroos are native to Australia\"}, {\"start\": 458.0, \"end\": 463.0, \"text\": \"and are prone to fighting.\"}, {\"start\": 466.0, \"end\": 470.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 470.0, \"end\": 474.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Rememberto like\"}, {\"start\": 475.0, \"end\": 477.0, \"text\": \"us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 477.024, \"end\": 484.024, \"text\": \"Sign1 News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "j7SziwCkoG4": {
    "video_id": "j7SziwCkoG4",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.27.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180128",
    "duration": 425,
    "view_count": 1169,
    "description": "1.27.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Trump returns from Davos to Russia bombshell\n-MeToo founder declines State of the Union invitation\n-FBI helping in search for missing 4-year old\n-Screw in boy's skull, millimeter away from death\n-Grammy awards preview\n-New Prince music coming\n\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Langu",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.92, \"end\": 6.96, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.96, \"end\": 9.12, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.12, \"end\": 10.68, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 10.68, \"end\": 13.34, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.2, \"end\": 25.94, \"text\": \"President Trump wrapped up his trip to the world economic forum in Davos yesterday and\"}, {\"start\": 25.94, \"end\": 32.42, \"text\": \"now returns to the United States to face yet another major development in the Russia investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 32.42, \"end\": 45.58, \"text\": \"It was revealed Thursday that President Trump instructed his White House counsel, Don McGahn,\"}, {\"start\": 45.58, \"end\": 49.32, \"text\": \"to fire special counsel Robert Mueller in June.\"}, {\"start\": 49.32, \"end\": 53.8, \"text\": \"McGahn refused and threatened to quit.\"}, {\"start\": 53.8, \"end\": 56.58, \"text\": \"The president eventually backed down.\"}, {\"start\": 56.58, \"end\": 64.42, \"text\": \"For months, White House aides and even the president himself denied that he ever considered\"}, {\"start\": 64.42, \"end\": 66.52, \"text\": \"firing Mueller.\"}, {\"start\": 66.52, \"end\": 73.56, \"text\": \"Two sources tell CNN Mueller now wants to interview the president as part of his Russia\"}, {\"start\": 73.56, \"end\": 79.32, \"text\": \"investigation and this week the president himself said he would welcome that opportunity.\"}, {\"start\": 81.92, \"end\": 92.26, \"text\": \"METOO founder Tarana Burke says she declined the White House's invitation to attend President\"}, {\"start\": 92.26, \"end\": 100.52, \"text\": \"Trump's State of the Union address on January 30th.\"}, {\"start\": 100.52, \"end\": 110.34, \"text\": \"Burke says two other sexual-harassment survivors declined as well.\"}, {\"start\": 110.42, \"end\": 118.48, \"text\": \"Instead, Burke says the three women are going to host their own \\\"State of Our Union\\\" event,\"}, {\"start\": 118.48, \"end\": 131.98, \"text\": \"to talk about women's issues and the solidarity that has grown among women since the Trump\"}, {\"start\": 131.98, \"end\": 133.86, \"text\": \"administration began.\"}, {\"start\": 136.16, \"end\": 146.94, \"text\": \"Four-year-old Raul Gonzalez Johnson was reported missing from his North Carolina home Wednesday\"}, {\"start\": 146.94, \"end\": 148.36, \"text\": \"morning.\"}, {\"start\": 148.36, \"end\": 152.2, \"text\": \"Now the FBI is stepping in to lead the search for him.\"}, {\"start\": 152.2, \"end\": 161.58, \"text\": \"Authorities don't know whether he wandered away or was the victim of foul play.\"}, {\"start\": 161.58, \"end\": 169.7, \"text\": \"Search teams scoured the area around his home Friday and the North Carolina State Highway\"}, {\"start\": 169.74, \"end\": 177.18, \"text\": \"Patrol set up roadblocks to canvas drivers.\"}, {\"start\": 177.18, \"end\": 182.5, \"text\": \"More than 40 law enforcement, search-and-rescue and volunteer agencies are involved in the\"}, {\"start\": 182.5, \"end\": 185.24, \"text\": \"search for the little boy.\"}, {\"start\": 186.8, \"end\": 201.06, \"text\": \"Thirteen-year-old Darius Foreman is recovery after a brush with death last weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 201.06, \"end\": 214.66, \"text\": \"Last Saturday, the Maryland boy was building a tree house when he fell from a branch and\"}, {\"start\": 214.66, \"end\": 219.16, \"text\": \"knocked over a wooden board that had a 6-inch screw in it.\"}, {\"start\": 219.16, \"end\": 222.8, \"text\": \"The board slammed down on his head and thrust the screw into his skull.\"}, {\"start\": 222.8, \"end\": 233.28, \"text\": \"First responders had to cut the board from 5-feet to 2-feet in order to get Darius into\"}, {\"start\": 233.28, \"end\": 236.24, \"text\": \"the ambulance.\"}, {\"start\": 236.24, \"end\": 245.68, \"text\": \"His mother says the rest of the board remained attached to his head for about seven hours.\"}, {\"start\": 245.68, \"end\": 256.48, \"text\": \"Doctors say he was just a millimeter away from bleeding to death.\"}, {\"start\": 256.48, \"end\": 265.52, \"text\": \"Darius is now recovering from a successful surgery and says he is going to keep the screw\"}, {\"start\": 265.52, \"end\": 269.24, \"text\": \"that nearly ended his life.\"}, {\"start\": 271.88, \"end\": 281.96, \"text\": \"The recording industry is getting ready to hand out its coveted Grammy awards this Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 281.96, \"end\": 288.08, \"text\": \"Rapper Jay-Z leads the pack in Grammy nominations.\"}, {\"start\": 288.08, \"end\": 291.52, \"text\": \"He's up for eight, including album of the year.\"}, {\"start\": 291.52, \"end\": 304.24, \"text\": \"Kendrick Lamarr and Bruno Mars came in second and third as the most nominated artists.\"}, {\"start\": 304.24, \"end\": 308.84, \"text\": \"Both are scheduled to perform at the show.\"}, {\"start\": 308.84, \"end\": 314.56, \"text\": \"The Grammys are already sending a strong message of diversity.\"}, {\"start\": 314.56, \"end\": 323.08, \"text\": \"This year, the seven most nominated artists are all people of color.\"}, {\"start\": 323.08, \"end\": 331.2, \"text\": \"And the song \\\"Despacito\\\" could make history as the first Spanish-language song ever to\"}, {\"start\": 331.2, \"end\": 334.4, \"text\": \"win song of the year.\"}, {\"start\": 334.4, \"end\": 339.6, \"text\": \"The Grammy awards air Sunday night on CBS.\"}, {\"start\": 342.12, \"end\": 351.16, \"text\": \"Prince fans around the world were devastated when the music superstar died of an accidental\"}, {\"start\": 351.16, \"end\": 356.32, \"text\": \"drug overdose in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 356.32, \"end\": 371.12, \"text\": \"But according to Variety magazine, members in charge of Prince's estate have unearthed\"}, {\"start\": 371.12, \"end\": 378.56, \"text\": \"dozens of unreleased songs hidden in a vault at his Paisley Park home.\"}, {\"start\": 378.56, \"end\": 385.84, \"text\": \"And soon fans will be able to listen to some of those never-heard-before songs.\"}, {\"start\": 385.84, \"end\": 393.92, \"text\": \"A spokesperson did not give many details about how many songs were discovered but he did\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 397.48, \"text\": \"say the music is \\\"mind blowing.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 398.96, \"end\": 401.44, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 401.44, \"end\": 403.08, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 403.08, \"end\": 405.32, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 405.32, \"end\": 410.12, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 410.32, \"end\": 417.72, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "oZDMo_ZKkcA": {
    "video_id": "oZDMo_ZKkcA",
    "title": "Will you get paid more? (ASL - 2.8.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180209",
    "duration": 86,
    "view_count": 144,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.78, \"end\": 7.76, \"text\": \"Your paycheck may go up this month, thanks to the new tax law.\"}, {\"start\": 7.76, \"end\": 13.3, \"text\": \"The Congressional Budget Office estimates employees will likely withhold between 10\"}, {\"start\": 13.38, \"end\": 17.22, \"text\": \"to 15 billion dollars less from workers every month.\"}, {\"start\": 17.22, \"end\": 21.16, \"text\": \"That means more money for you.\"}, {\"start\": 21.16, \"end\": 29.46, \"text\": \"Payroll service ADP crunched the numbers.\"}, {\"start\": 29.46, \"end\": 36.66, \"text\": \"Let's say you are a single filer, getting paid twice a month, taking one withholding\"}, {\"start\": 36.66, \"end\": 44.84, \"text\": \"allowance, contributing 5 percent to a 401(k) and making 57,000 dollars a year.\"}, {\"start\": 44.84, \"end\": 48.18, \"text\": \"You can see 60 dollars more in your check.\"}, {\"start\": 48.18, \"end\": 55.68, \"text\": \"If you make about 162,000 dollars a year, expect to see about 190 dollars more.\"}, {\"start\": 55.68, \"end\": 64.14, \"text\": \"Let's look at married workers to file jointly, put 5 percent in a 401(k), get paid every\"}, {\"start\": 64.14, \"end\": 66.7, \"text\": \"two weeks but take two allowances.\"}, {\"start\": 66.7, \"end\": 73.18, \"text\": \"The joint filer making 61,000 dollars could see an extra 40 bucks a pay period.\"}, {\"start\": 73.26, \"end\": 79.0, \"text\": \"Remember your take-home pay depends on much more than just your salary and allowances.\"}, {\"start\": 79.0, \"end\": 83.52, \"text\": \"State and local taxes as well as health deductions may also impact your pay and could eat up\"}, {\"start\": 83.52, \"end\": 85.5, \"text\": \"any potential extra cash.\"}]"
  },
  "cJyKY1fsm4Q": {
    "video_id": "cJyKY1fsm4Q",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.15.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180216",
    "duration": 379,
    "view_count": 2012,
    "description": "2.15.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Florida school shooting update\n-One victim is being called a hero\n-What do recent mass shootings in America have in common?\n-U.S. officials warn about smartphones made in China\n-Strong winds in S. Korea cause damage during the Olympic games\n-Compassion may lead to happiness\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and in",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.92, \"end\": 8.92, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.92, \"end\": 11.02, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.02, \"end\": 12.26, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.26, \"end\": 15.68, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.86, \"end\": 29.86, \"text\": \"Police say 19-year old Nikolas Cruz opened fire on students at Marjory Stoneman Douglas high school\"}, {\"start\": 29.86, \"end\": 30.98, \"text\": \"yesterday.\"}, {\"start\": 31.12, \"end\": 37.3, \"text\": \"Today Cruz made his first court appearance today in Fort Lauderdale.\"}, {\"start\": 37.34, \"end\": 45.34, \"text\": \"Cruz is charged with 17 counts of premeditated murder.\"}, {\"start\": 45.34, \"end\": 50.24, \"text\": \"At least 17 people died and at least 14 others were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 50.24, \"end\": 58.18, \"text\": \"Investigators say Cruz pulled the school's fire alarm to draw people out and then opened\"}, {\"start\": 58.18, \"end\": 62.72, \"text\": \"fire on them using an AR-15 style firearm.\"}, {\"start\": 62.72, \"end\": 72.34, \"text\": \"Prosecutors asked for Cruz to be held without bond and the defense did not argue against it.\"}, {\"start\": 72.34, \"end\": 77.24, \"text\": \"In his address, today President Trump says he's committed to making schools safer and\"}, {\"start\": 77.24, \"end\": 81.46, \"text\": \"tackling the issue of mental health.\"}, {\"start\": 81.46, \"end\": 85.24, \"text\": \"However he did not mention gun control.\"}, {\"start\": 88.32, \"end\": 100.8, \"text\": \"One of the victims in the shooting, assistant football coach and security guard Aaron Feis,\"}, {\"start\": 100.8, \"end\": 103.5, \"text\": \"is being hailed a hero.\"}, {\"start\": 103.5, \"end\": 109.59, \"text\": \"When the shooting started, officials say Feis threw himself in front of students to shield\"}, {\"start\": 109.59, \"end\": 113.65, \"text\": \"them from bullets.\"}, {\"start\": 113.65, \"end\": 118.24, \"text\": \"He was rushed to the hospital and into surgery but later died from his injuries.\"}, {\"start\": 118.24, \"end\": 126.64, \"text\": \"Because the school is now crime scene, it is closed until further notice.\"}, {\"start\": 129.3, \"end\": 135.84, \"text\": \"Many of the worst mass shootings in recent years have something in common: The same weapon,\"}, {\"start\": 135.84, \"end\": 140.24, \"text\": \"the AR-15 rifle, was used in all of the shootings.\"}, {\"start\": 140.24, \"end\": 151.36, \"text\": \"The Sutherland Springs church, the Las Vegas country music concert, Pulse nightclub, the\"}, {\"start\": 151.36, \"end\": 169.68, \"text\": \"San Bernardino office shooting, Sandy Hook elementary and the Aurora movie theater.\"}, {\"start\": 169.68, \"end\": 179.92, \"text\": \"The National Rifle Association says the AR-15 is adaptable, reliable and accurate.\"}, {\"start\": 179.92, \"end\": 186.96, \"text\": \"The NRA says the AR-15 is America's most popular rifle.\"}, {\"start\": 186.96, \"end\": 190.32, \"text\": \"It is owned by more than 8 million people in this country.\"}, {\"start\": 193.2, \"end\": 202.4, \"text\": \"US intelligence agencies have issued a stern warning to Americans: Do not buy smart phones\"}, {\"start\": 202.4, \"end\": 209.68, \"text\": \"made by Chinese tech companies Huawei or Zte.\"}, {\"start\": 209.68, \"end\": 220.72, \"text\": \"Top officials from the CIA, NSA, FBI and the Defense Intelligence Agency testified in front\"}, {\"start\": 220.72, \"end\": 227.6, \"text\": \"of the Senate intelligence committee on Tuesday that the Chinese smartphone makers pose a\"}, {\"start\": 227.6, \"end\": 230.72, \"text\": \"security threat to American customers.\"}, {\"start\": 233.76, \"end\": 245.04, \"text\": \"North Korea's cheering squad attended Thursday's race in the giant slalom, which had been delayed\"}, {\"start\": 245.04, \"end\": 249.52, \"text\": \"two days due to wind.\"}, {\"start\": 249.52, \"end\": 257.6, \"text\": \"The group waved flags representing a unified Korea and sang songs celebrating the lunar\"}, {\"start\": 257.6, \"end\": 260.32, \"text\": \"new year as they watched.\"}, {\"start\": 260.32, \"end\": 268.88, \"text\": \"American Mikaela Shiffrin claimed Olympic gold.\"}, {\"start\": 268.88, \"end\": 274.88, \"text\": \"This is her second victory in the slalom after winning her first goal in Sochi at age 18.\"}, {\"start\": 277.52, \"end\": 285.28, \"text\": \"A study shows if you are looking for ways to be happier and make deeper connections\"}, {\"start\": 285.28, \"end\": 291.09, \"text\": \"with the people in your life, try being a little more compassionate.\"}, {\"start\": 291.09, \"end\": 296.02, \"text\": \"Compassion is related to empathy and has been described as a feeling of kindness towards\"}, {\"start\": 296.02, \"end\": 297.85, \"text\": \"other people.\"}, {\"start\": 297.85, \"end\": 305.6, \"text\": \"A University of Miami professor says compassionate people tend to be more forgiving of others\"}, {\"start\": 305.6, \"end\": 309.2, \"text\": \"and have a strong sense of life purpose.\"}, {\"start\": 309.2, \"end\": 314.16, \"text\": \"They are also more self-confident and more resilient.\"}, {\"start\": 314.16, \"end\": 317.44, \"text\": \"So how do you become more compassionate?\"}, {\"start\": 317.44, \"end\": 321.04, \"text\": \"Daily meditation is a great way to start and can have lasting benefits.\"}, {\"start\": 321.04, \"end\": 329.04, \"text\": \"Take about 10 to 20 minutes and find a quiet place to clear your mind.\"}, {\"start\": 329.04, \"end\": 334.96, \"text\": \"Focus on different people -- those you are close to as well as those you aren't -- and\"}, {\"start\": 334.96, \"end\": 336.8, \"text\": \"think positively about them.\"}, {\"start\": 336.8, \"end\": 342.64, \"text\": \"Exercises like this can strengthen your sense of compassion as well as broaden your attention\"}, {\"start\": 342.64, \"end\": 346.56, \"text\": \"and your overall sense of well-being.\"}, {\"start\": 348.82, \"end\": 351.3, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 351.3, \"end\": 352.62, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 352.62, \"end\": 355.22, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 355.22, \"end\": 360.32, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 360.32, \"end\": 366.46, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "bA3PhnWe0gM": {
    "video_id": "bA3PhnWe0gM",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.14.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171115",
    "duration": 616,
    "view_count": 311,
    "description": "November 14, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-4 PEOPLE KILLED IN CALIFORNIA SHOOTING\n-JEFF SESSIONS GRILLED ON CAPITOL HILL\n-TRUMP WRAPS UP ASIA TRIP \n-SANDY HOOK LAWSUIT HEARING\n-UCLA BASKETBALL PLAYERS RELEASED FROM CHINA\n-STOVE TOP SELLING THANKSGIVING PANTS\n-JORDIN SPARKS MARRIED, EXPECTING FIRST BABY\n-MILITARY WIDOW REVEALS BABY'S GENDER ON VETERAN'S DAY\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 10.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.024, \"end\": 14.024, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau. And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.0, \"end\": 22.0, \"text\": \"Four people are dead in Rancho Tehama,\"}, {\"start\": 22.0, \"end\": 27.0, \"text\": \"California. Investigators say a\"}, {\"start\": 27.0, \"end\": 31.0, \"text\": \"gunman went on a shooting spree in seven different\"}, {\"start\": 31.0, \"end\": 36.0, \"text\": \"locations. He ended up at an elementary school where\"}, {\"start\": 36.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"police confronted him and killed him. At least one student\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 47.0, \"text\": \"was shot at the school and a child was shot in a car.\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"Police believe the violence started with a domestic\"}, {\"start\": 53.0, \"end\": 57.0, \"text\": \"dispute and then spread across town.\"}, {\"start\": 58.0, \"end\": 62.0, \"text\": \"Police recovered a semi-automatic\"}, {\"start\": 63.0, \"end\": 68.0, \"text\": \"rifle and two handguns\"}, {\"start\": 68.0, \"end\": 71.0, \"text\": \"believed to be used by the shooter.\"}, {\"start\": 72.0, \"end\": 76.0, \"text\": \"The gunman's identity has not yet been released.\"}, {\"start\": 79.0, \"end\": 83.0, \"text\": \"Attorney General Jeff Sessions\"}, {\"start\": 84.0, \"end\": 88.0, \"text\": \"was in the hot seat for\"}, {\"start\": 88.0, \"end\": 93.0, \"text\": \"hours Tuesday answering questions from the House\"}, {\"start\": 94.0, \"end\": 98.0, \"text\": \"Judiciary Committee.\"}, {\"start\": 99.0, \"end\": 103.0, \"text\": \"Lawmakers asked him about many topics\"}, {\"start\": 103.0, \"end\": 106.0, \"text\": \"including the Russia investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 107.0, \"end\": 112.0, \"text\": \"Sessions was adamant when he said he never lied under\"}, {\"start\": 113.0, \"end\": 118.0, \"text\": \"oath regarding what he knew and when he knew it about the\"}, {\"start\": 118.0, \"end\": 121.0, \"text\": \"interactions between the Trump campaign and Russia.\"}, {\"start\": 122.0, \"end\": 126.0, \"text\": \"There were also some questions about a possible\"}, {\"start\": 127.0, \"end\": 132.0, \"text\": \"investigation into Hillary Clinton and her handling of\"}, {\"start\": 132.0, \"end\": 136.0, \"text\": \"classified documents when she was Secretary of State.\"}, {\"start\": 137.0, \"end\": 142.0, \"text\": \"Sessions declined to reveal whether there is an ongoing investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 145.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"President Trump is back in Washington after a 12 day tour of\"}, {\"start\": 151.0, \"end\": 156.0, \"text\": \"Asia. He called the trip a smashing success.\"}, {\"start\": 156.0, \"end\": 161.0, \"text\": \"He said he had a wonderful welcome in Japan and South\"}, {\"start\": 161.0, \"end\": 166.0, \"text\": \"Korea and the red carpet was\"}, {\"start\": 166.0, \"end\": 171.0, \"text\": \"rolled out for him in China.\"}, {\"start\": 172.0, \"end\": 176.0, \"text\": \"He said he is most proud of the progress he made\"}, {\"start\": 177.0, \"end\": 181.0, \"text\": \"in terms of strengthening relations with Asia's leaders and establishing\"}, {\"start\": 181.0, \"end\": 186.0, \"text\": \"trade agreements. White House officials say that Trump\"}, {\"start\": 187.0, \"end\": 192.0, \"text\": \"will be giving a speech either Wednesday or Thursday\"}, {\"start\": 192.0, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"to talk about what he was able to accomplish during\"}, {\"start\": 196.0, \"end\": 199.0, \"text\": \"his 12 day tour of Asia.\"}, {\"start\": 202.0, \"end\": 210.0, \"text\": \"Lawyers for the victims of the 2012\"}, {\"start\": 210.0, \"end\": 218.0, \"text\": \"Newtown shooting are asking the\"}, {\"start\": 218.1, \"end\": 226.1, \"text\": \"Connecticut Supreme Court to reinstate\"}, {\"start\": 226.1, \"end\": 234.1, \"text\": \"a wrongful death lawsuit against\"}, {\"start\": 234.1, \"end\": 237.1, \"text\": \"Remington Arms.\"}, {\"start\": 237.1, \"end\": 241.0, \"text\": \"They are the maker of the\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 246.0, \"text\": \"AR-15 style rifle used in the\"}, {\"start\": 246.0, \"end\": 252.0, \"text\": \"Sandy Hook elementary school shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 252.0, \"end\": 257.0, \"text\": \"The families of the victims say Remington\"}, {\"start\": 257.0, \"end\": 264.0, \"text\": \"Arms knowingly sold a military\"}, {\"start\": 264.0, \"end\": 267.0, \"text\": \"weapon to civilians.\"}, {\"start\": 268.0, \"end\": 274.0, \"text\": \"Adam Lanza used the AR-15\"}, {\"start\": 274.0, \"end\": 279.0, \"text\": \"to shoot and kill his mother and then went to the elementary school\"}, {\"start\": 279.0, \"end\": 283.0, \"text\": \"and shot 20 first graders,\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 290.0, \"text\": \"six educators and then himself.\"}, {\"start\": 290.0, \"end\": 294.0, \"text\": \"The first lawsuit was filed in 2015\"}, {\"start\": 294.0, \"end\": 302.0, \"text\": \"but was dismissed in 2016 by a lower court.\"}, {\"start\": 306.024, \"end\": 309.924, \"text\": \"Three UCLA men's basketball players\"}, {\"start\": 310.0, \"end\": 315.0, \"text\": \"detained in China are returning to the United States and\"}, {\"start\": 315.0, \"end\": 319.0, \"text\": \"they may have President Trump to thank.\"}, {\"start\": 320.0, \"end\": 324.0, \"text\": \"The commissioner of the Pacific 12 Athletic\"}, {\"start\": 324.0, \"end\": 330.0, \"text\": \"Conference says LiAngelo\"}, {\"start\": 330.0, \"end\": 335.0, \"text\": \"Ball, Jalen Hill\"}, {\"start\": 335.0, \"end\": 340.0, \"text\": \"and Cody Riley boarded a flight\"}, {\"start\": 340.0, \"end\": 345.0, \"text\": \"Tuesday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 345.0, \"end\": 350.0, \"text\": \"The commissioner says the three were allowed\"}, {\"start\": 350.0, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"to leave after the situation was resolved to\"}, {\"start\": 354.0, \"end\": 356.0, \"text\": \"the satisfaction of Chinese authorities.\"}, {\"start\": 356.924, \"end\": 359.924, \"text\": \"The three freshmen were part of the UCLA\"}, {\"start\": 360.0, \"end\": 365.0, \"text\": \"squad in China for a basketball game against Georgia Tech last week.\"}, {\"start\": 365.0, \"end\": 370.0, \"text\": \"They were accused of shoplifting\"}, {\"start\": 370.0, \"end\": 374.0, \"text\": \"designer sunglasses from a\"}, {\"start\": 374.0, \"end\": 379.0, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton store. While President Trump was\"}, {\"start\": 379.0, \"end\": 384.0, \"text\": \"in China there are reports that he asked Chinese\"}, {\"start\": 384.0, \"end\": 388.0, \"text\": \"President Xi Jinping for a quick resolution to the\"}, {\"start\": 388.0, \"end\": 392.0, \"text\": \"case. The three players are expected to speak to the media\"}, {\"start\": 393.0, \"end\": 400.0, \"text\": \"Wednesday in Los Angeles.\"}, {\"start\": 402.0, \"end\": 405.0, \"text\": \"Thanksgiving just got a little easier for people who like\"}, {\"start\": 405.0, \"end\": 412.0, \"text\": \"to go back for seconds -- and even thirds.\"}, {\"start\": 413.0, \"end\": 416.0, \"text\": \"Stove Top Stuffing has\"}, {\"start\": 416.0, \"end\": 421.0, \"text\": \"designed these fashionable\"}, {\"start\": 421.0, \"end\": 428.0, \"text\": \"unisex pants with an elastic waist band.\"}, {\"start\": 428.0, \"end\": 434.0, \"text\": \"An image of the stuffing is placed high and fits right over your belly.\"}, {\"start\": 434.024, \"end\": 435.999, \"text\": \"Stove Top says it wants to allow people to\"}, {\"start\": 436.0, \"end\": 441.0, \"text\": \"enjoy more of Thanksgiving in comfort and style.\"}, {\"start\": 441.0, \"end\": 449.0, \"text\": \"It will cost you about 20 bucks while supplies last\"}, {\"start\": 449.0, \"end\": 452.0, \"text\": \"Okay...the pants may not be so\"}, {\"start\": 452.0, \"end\": 457.0, \"text\": \"flattering but they are for a good cause.\"}, {\"start\": 458.0, \"end\": 463.0, \"text\": \"Stove Top is donating $10,000 of the proceeds to the\"}, {\"start\": 463.0, \"end\": 470.0, \"text\": \"Feeding America charity.\"}, {\"start\": 470.024, \"end\": 475.924, \"text\": \"Congratulations to former American Idol\"}, {\"start\": 476.0, \"end\": 483.0, \"text\": \"winner Jordin Sparks.\"}, {\"start\": 483.0, \"end\": 487.0, \"text\": \"The 27 year old confirmed she secretly wed\"}, {\"start\": 487.0, \"end\": 495.0, \"text\": \"boyfriend Dana Isaiah in July.\"}, {\"start\": 495.0, \"end\": 498.0, \"text\": \"The two eloped while on vacation in\"}, {\"start\": 498.0, \"end\": 504.0, \"text\": \"Hawaii with a few friends.\"}, {\"start\": 504.0, \"end\": 507.0, \"text\": \"Not only that but the two are expecting\"}, {\"start\": 507.0, \"end\": 512.0, \"text\": \"their first child in the spring. They learned the happy news just a\"}, {\"start\": 512.0, \"end\": 517.0, \"text\": \"few weeks after getting married. Sparks says she's now\"}, {\"start\": 517.0, \"end\": 522.0, \"text\": \"counting her blessings and welcoming the changes in her life.\"}, {\"start\": 524.001, \"end\": 527.001, \"text\": \"A Michigan woman chose\"}, {\"start\": 527.1, \"end\": 531.0, \"text\": \"Veteran's Day to reveal\"}, {\"start\": 531.0, \"end\": 535.0, \"text\": \"the gender of her baby.\"}, {\"start\": 535.0, \"end\": 539.0, \"text\": \"Cassie Lohrey's husband\"}, {\"start\": 539.0, \"end\": 544.0, \"text\": \"Ryan was in the Navy. He died in a\"}, {\"start\": 544.0, \"end\": 549.0, \"text\": \"military plane crash in July.\"}, {\"start\": 549.0, \"end\": 554.0, \"text\": \"The couple had discussed the idea of having children\"}, {\"start\": 554.0, \"end\": 559.0, \"text\": \"but it wasn't until after her husband died Lohrey found out she was expecting.\"}, {\"start\": 559.0, \"end\": 564.0, \"text\": \"So she gathered a group of Marine and Navy friends who served with her husband\"}, {\"start\": 564.0, \"end\": 569.0, \"text\": \"to help her reveal the baby's gender in grand fashion.\"}, {\"start\": 569.0, \"end\": 573.0, \"text\": \"The baby girl is due in March and will be\"}, {\"start\": 573.0, \"end\": 581.0, \"text\": \"named Ryan in honor of her father.\"}, {\"start\": 581.001, \"end\": 588.001, \"text\": \"A Go Fund Me page has been set up to help with the expenses.\"}, {\"start\": 590.0, \"end\": 594.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 594.0, \"end\": 598.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Remember to like us on Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 598.0, \"end\": 602.0, \"text\": \"and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 603.024, \"end\": 609.024, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "oHbQ-L2nwk8": {
    "video_id": "oHbQ-L2nwk8",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.20.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171021",
    "duration": 481,
    "view_count": 157,
    "description": "October 20, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-WHAT REALLY HAPPENED IN NIGER?\n-AFRICAN AMERICAN MAN HUGS MAN WEARING NAZI SWASTIKAS\n-MELANIA DONATES INAUGURAL GOWN TO SMITHSONIAN\n-BURGER KING TAKES ON BULLYING IN AD\n-TYLER PERRY'S 'BOO 2! A MADEA HALLOWEEN'\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSIT",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Candace\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 15.0, \"text\": \"Jones. And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.0, \"end\": 23.0, \"text\": \"Earlier this month four U.S. soldiers were killed in an ambush\"}, {\"start\": 23.0, \"end\": 28.0, \"text\": \"attack in Niger, Africa.\"}, {\"start\": 28.0, \"end\": 33.0, \"text\": \"The Pentagon and the FBI are now joining\"}, {\"start\": 33.0, \"end\": 37.0, \"text\": \"forces to figure out what happened.\"}, {\"start\": 38.0, \"end\": 42.0, \"text\": \"Here's what they know so far.\"}, {\"start\": 42.0, \"end\": 49.0, \"text\": \"The soldiers were leading a 12 man team\"}, {\"start\": 49.0, \"end\": 54.0, \"text\": \"to visit village elders.\"}, {\"start\": 54.1, \"end\": 59.1, \"text\": \"They had done 29 patrols prior to this one with\"}, {\"start\": 60.0, \"end\": 65.0, \"text\": \"no problems. And they had been told it was\"}, {\"start\": 65.0, \"end\": 69.0, \"text\": \"unlikely there would be any enemies in the area.\"}, {\"start\": 69.0, \"end\": 73.0, \"text\": \"But when the soldiers went back to their vehicle\"}, {\"start\": 73.0, \"end\": 77.0, \"text\": \"they walked into an ambush.\"}, {\"start\": 77.0, \"end\": 82.0, \"text\": \"Fifty ISIS fighters were waiting with guns and\"}, {\"start\": 84.0, \"end\": 89.0, \"text\": \"rocket propelled grenades.\"}, {\"start\": 90.0, \"end\": 94.0, \"text\": \"All the soldiers had were rifles.\"}, {\"start\": 95.0, \"end\": 99.0, \"text\": \"It took nearly an hour before a helicopter\"}, {\"start\": 100.0, \"end\": 107.0, \"text\": \"came to get the dead and the wounded.\"}, {\"start\": 107.0, \"end\": 112.0, \"text\": \"And the helicopter ended up leaving one\"}, {\"start\": 112.0, \"end\": 114.0, \"text\": \"dead soldier behind.\"}, {\"start\": 117.0, \"end\": 121.0, \"text\": \"Yesterday we showed you the massive protest at the\"}, {\"start\": 121.0, \"end\": 126.0, \"text\": \"University of Florida. Hundreds of people\"}, {\"start\": 126.0, \"end\": 130.0, \"text\": \"were upset because the school allowed Richard\"}, {\"start\": 131.0, \"end\": 138.0, \"text\": \"Spencer, a white supremacist,\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 144.0, \"text\": \"to speak on campus.\"}, {\"start\": 144.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"But during the yelling and screaming someone videotaped\"}, {\"start\": 149.0, \"end\": 152.0, \"text\": \"an unusual sight.\"}, {\"start\": 152.0, \"end\": 156.0, \"text\": \"It shows an African American man\"}, {\"start\": 160.0, \"end\": 165.0, \"text\": \"hugging a white man.\"}, {\"start\": 165.0, \"end\": 173.0, \"text\": \"The white man was wearing a shirt with Nazi swastikas.\"}, {\"start\": 173.0, \"end\": 178.0, \"text\": \"You can hear the African American man\"}, {\"start\": 181.0, \"end\": 186.0, \"text\": \"asking the white man why he doesn't like  him.\"}, {\"start\": 186.0, \"end\": 191.0, \"text\": \"However we found out later another random\"}, {\"start\": 191.0, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"protester punched the white guy.\"}, {\"start\": 196.0, \"end\": 200.0, \"text\": \"Police had to remove the white man from the protest\"}, {\"start\": 201.0, \"end\": 204.0, \"text\": \"to keep him safe.\"}, {\"start\": 206.0, \"end\": 211.0, \"text\": \"Today first lady MelaniaTrump\"}, {\"start\": 211.0, \"end\": 216.0, \"text\": \"donated her 2017 inaugural ball gown\"}, {\"start\": 216.0, \"end\": 221.0, \"text\": \"to the Smithsonian's National Museum\"}, {\"start\": 222.0, \"end\": 226.0, \"text\": \"of American history.\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 230.0, \"text\": \"The dress designer\"}, {\"start\": 231.0, \"end\": 237.0, \"text\": \"Herve Pierre was also at the ceremony.\"}, {\"start\": 237.0, \"end\": 242.0, \"text\": \"Collecting first day inaugural gowns is a long\"}, {\"start\": 242.0, \"end\": 247.0, \"text\": \"standing tradition.\"}, {\"start\": 247.0, \"end\": 252.0, \"text\": \"The first dress donated was from First Lady\"}, {\"start\": 252.0, \"end\": 260.0, \"text\": \"Helen Taft in 1912.\"}, {\"start\": 260.0, \"end\": 263.0, \"text\": \"The gown exhibit is one of the museum's\"}, {\"start\": 264.0, \"end\": 269.0, \"text\": \"most popular tourist attraction.\"}, {\"start\": 270.0, \"end\": 275.0, \"text\": \"Last year an estimated 4 million visitors\"}, {\"start\": 275.001, \"end\": 276.001, \"text\": \"passed through\"}, {\"start\": 276.1, \"end\": 284.1, \"text\": \"the first lady's exhibit.\"}, {\"start\": 290.024, \"end\": 292.024, \"text\": \"October is National Bullying\"}, {\"start\": 293.0, \"end\": 294.0, \"text\": \"Prevention Month.\"}, {\"start\": 295.0, \"end\": 298.0, \"text\": \"Burger King has just released a new video to support\"}, {\"start\": 298.0, \"end\": 303.0, \"text\": \"anti-bullying.\"}, {\"start\": 303.0, \"end\": 308.0, \"text\": \"Burger King videotaped a bullying experiment to see what people would do.\"}, {\"start\": 308.0, \"end\": 313.0, \"text\": \"The company hired teenaged actors to act out bullying on\"}, {\"start\": 313.0, \"end\": 318.0, \"text\": \"another teen at one of their stores.\"}, {\"start\": 318.0, \"end\": 322.0, \"text\": \"To the real customers it looked\"}, {\"start\": 326.0, \"end\": 331.0, \"text\": \"like real bullying but very few people spoke up\"}, {\"start\": 331.024, \"end\": 336.924, \"text\": \"or tried to help.\"}, {\"start\": 337.0, \"end\": 341.0, \"text\": \"Behind the counter actors playing\"}, {\"start\": 341.0, \"end\": 346.0, \"text\": \"employees served punched\"}, {\"start\": 346.0, \"end\": 351.0, \"text\": \"and mangled burgers to customers. The customers\"}, {\"start\": 353.0, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"quickly spoke up.\"}, {\"start\": 354.0, \"end\": 358.0, \"text\": \"Burger King's message: Be as willing to speak up\"}, {\"start\": 360.0, \"end\": 365.0, \"text\": \"about a bullied person as you are\"}, {\"start\": 365.0, \"end\": 369.0, \"text\": \"about a bullied hamburger.\"}, {\"start\": 372.0, \"end\": 376.0, \"text\": \"Tyler Perry's\"}, {\"start\": 376.024, \"end\": 382.024, \"text\": \"new movie \\\"Boo 2\\\" is in theaters now.\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 386.0, \"text\": \"The first Madea Halloween movie was released last year\"}, {\"start\": 387.0, \"end\": 392.0, \"text\": \"and raked in over\"}, {\"start\": 393.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"74 million dollars. Perry says it was the second\"}, {\"start\": 398.0, \"end\": 406.0, \"text\": \"biggest Madea movie ever made.\"}, {\"start\": 408.001, \"end\": 411.001, \"text\": \"So Perry decided to make another\"}, {\"start\": 412.0, \"end\": 416.0, \"text\": \"Madea Halloween movie this year.\"}, {\"start\": 416.0, \"end\": 420.0, \"text\": \"And he says he's already working on two more movies.\"}, {\"start\": 421.0, \"end\": 424.0, \"text\": \"One is entitled\"}, {\"start\": 424.024, \"end\": 426.924, \"text\": \"A Madea\"}, {\"start\": 427.0, \"end\": 434.0, \"text\": \"Family Funeral.\"}, {\"start\": 434.001, \"end\": 439.001, \"text\": \"The other is entitled Acrimony.\"}, {\"start\": 439.2, \"end\": 444.0, \"text\": \"It stars actress\"}, {\"start\": 444.0, \"end\": 449.0, \"text\": \"Taraji P. Henson.\"}, {\"start\": 449.0, \"end\": 453.0, \"text\": \"Both movies will be released next year.\"}, {\"start\": 456.024, \"end\": 459.024, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.  I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 459.1, \"end\": 462.1, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 462.1, \"end\": 466.1, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us onTwitter.\"}, {\"start\": 467.0, \"end\": 473.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "iMYQVqkvJ_s": {
    "video_id": "iMYQVqkvJ_s",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.1.18: News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180202",
    "duration": 475,
    "view_count": 987,
    "description": "2.1.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-California school shooting latest\n-White House and FBI clash over memo\n-Oprah cuts Russell Simmons from book\n-Coffee may come with a warning in California\n-Hasbro announces Monopoly Cheaters Edition game\n-Super Bowl ad: Wendy’s mocks McDonald's\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Langu",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.04, \"end\": 9.18, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.18, \"end\": 11.26, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.26, \"end\": 12.78, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.78, \"end\": 15.82, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.98, \"end\": 27.62, \"text\": \"Investigators are trying to figure out what caused a 12-year-old girl to open fire in\"}, {\"start\": 27.62, \"end\": 31.28, \"text\": \"a Los Angeles middle school classroom Thursday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 31.28, \"end\": 36.74, \"text\": \"Officers received a 9-1-1 call from Sal Castro Middle School just before 9 AM.\"}, {\"start\": 36.78, \"end\": 41.74, \"text\": \"When they arrived, they discovered two 15-year-old students had been shot.\"}, {\"start\": 41.74, \"end\": 45.72, \"text\": \"A boy had a shot in the head and is listed in critical condition.\"}, {\"start\": 45.72, \"end\": 49.12, \"text\": \"A girl was shot in the wrist.\"}, {\"start\": 49.28, \"end\": 56.2, \"text\": \"Three others are being treated for minor cuts from broken glass.\"}, {\"start\": 56.2, \"end\": 62.28, \"text\": \"Police arrested a 12-year-old girl and confiscated a semi-automatic gun at the scene.\"}, {\"start\": 62.28, \"end\": 65.48, \"text\": \"The school was briefly put on lockdown to make sure there was no further safety threats\"}, {\"start\": 65.48, \"end\": 67.88, \"text\": \"to students and staff.\"}, {\"start\": 67.88, \"end\": 72.2, \"text\": \"The school has since reopened and counselors brought in to help students deal with the\"}, {\"start\": 72.4, \"end\": 76.24, \"text\": \"trauma.\"}, {\"start\": 76.24, \"end\": 80.68, \"text\": \"A motive for the shooting is still under investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 83.92, \"end\": 89.2, \"text\": \"There is a rift between the White House and the FBI.\"}, {\"start\": 89.36, \"end\": 93.56, \"text\": \"And it's all over a 4-page memo.\"}, {\"start\": 93.56, \"end\": 100.6, \"text\": \"It's a report from the House Intelligence Committee compilei by Republican Congressman\"}, {\"start\": 100.88, \"end\": 103.16, \"text\": \"Devon Nunes.\"}, {\"start\": 103.16, \"end\": 114.44, \"text\": \"The report accuses the FBI of abusing surveillance powers.\"}, {\"start\": 114.48, \"end\": 119.92, \"text\": \"President Trump wants it released ASAP.\"}, {\"start\": 120.04, \"end\": 129.76, \"text\": \"But FBI director Christopher Wray is concerned about the memo's contents.\"}, {\"start\": 129.88, \"end\": 135.72, \"text\": \"The FBI took a stand against the president by putting out a statement that said:\"}, {\"start\": 135.72, \"end\": 140.4, \"text\": \"\\\"The FBI was provided a limited opportunity to review this memo.\"}, {\"start\": 140.4, \"end\": 145.96, \"text\": \"We have grave concerns about material omissions of fact that fundamentally impact the memo's\"}, {\"start\": 145.96, \"end\": 148.44, \"text\": \"accuracy.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 148.44, \"end\": 156.36, \"text\": \"Nunes issued his own statement defending the memo, saying it will help \\\"ensure our intelligence\"}, {\"start\": 156.36, \"end\": 160.24, \"text\": \"agencies and courts are never misuse like this again.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 160.24, \"end\": 165.64, \"text\": \"But critics say those who support the memo's release want to undermine special counsel\"}, {\"start\": 165.68, \"end\": 169.84, \"text\": \"Robert Mueller's Russian investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 169.84, \"end\": 178.52, \"text\": \"And Democratic Congressman Adam Schiff claims Nunes made changes to the memo before sending\"}, {\"start\": 178.56, \"end\": 181.8, \"text\": \"it to the White House.\"}, {\"start\": 181.8, \"end\": 188.04, \"text\": \"Nunes says the changes were \\\"minor edits.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 188.04, \"end\": 192.88, \"text\": \"The White House will complete a full review before it decides whether or not the memo\"}, {\"start\": 192.88, \"end\": 194.64, \"text\": \"is released.\"}, {\"start\": 197.04, \"end\": 201.96, \"text\": \"Russell Simmons' thoughts on meditation, wealth and the soul will no longer be part of Oprah\"}, {\"start\": 201.96, \"end\": 205.24, \"text\": \"Winfrey's upcoming spiritual advice book.\"}, {\"start\": 205.24, \"end\": 223.52, \"text\": \"The book entitled \\\"The Wisdom of Sundays\\\" feature conversations between Winfrey and\"}, {\"start\": 223.52, \"end\": 231.52, \"text\": \"other celebrities.\"}, {\"start\": 231.52, \"end\": 234.8, \"text\": \"But the New York Times now reports Winfrey and the books publisher are dropping Simmons'\"}, {\"start\": 234.8, \"end\": 237.12, \"text\": \"passage from future editions of the book after multiple women accused him of rape and sexual\"}, {\"start\": 237.12, \"end\": 240.4, \"text\": \"misconduct.\"}, {\"start\": 242.96, \"end\": 251.76, \"text\": \"Your morning coffee might soon come with a warning in California.\"}, {\"start\": 251.76, \"end\": 260.96, \"text\": \"The state keeps a list of chemicals it considers possible causes of cancer, and one of them,\"}, {\"start\": 260.96, \"end\": 271.04, \"text\": \"acrylamide, is created when coffee beans are roasted.\"}, {\"start\": 271.04, \"end\": 280.4, \"text\": \"The lawsuit filed in Los Angeles targets companies that make or sell coffee.\"}, {\"start\": 280.4, \"end\": 285.52, \"text\": \"According to the suit, the defendants \\\"failed to provide clear and readable warning\\\" that\"}, {\"start\": 285.52, \"end\": 289.44, \"text\": \"drinking coffee could expose people to acrylamide.\"}, {\"start\": 289.44, \"end\": 294.88, \"text\": \"The suit seeks to impose fines and force the companies to post warnings.\"}, {\"start\": 295.12, \"end\": 303.44, \"text\": \"The companies argue that acrylamide levels in coffee should be considered safe under\"}, {\"start\": 303.44, \"end\": 315.84, \"text\": \"state law and that the health benefits of coffee outweigh the risks.\"}, {\"start\": 315.84, \"end\": 322.72, \"text\": \"At least 13 of the defendants have settled and agreed to give a warning.\"}, {\"start\": 322.72, \"end\": 332.16, \"text\": \"Retailers that haven't already settled will meet for private mediation on February 8th.\"}, {\"start\": 334.96, \"end\": 346.789, \"text\": \"Monopoly is releasing a special \\\"cheaters\\\" edition of the classic game.\"}, {\"start\": 346.8, \"end\": 354.96, \"text\": \"In this version fans are encouraged to play dirty.\"}, {\"start\": 354.96, \"end\": 358.56, \"text\": \"The goal is to not get caught.\"}, {\"start\": 358.56, \"end\": 363.2, \"text\": \"The new game will include several tasks for players to complete.\"}, {\"start\": 363.2, \"end\": 369.28, \"text\": \"If you can successfully cheat your way to getting the task done, you'll get rewards.\"}, {\"start\": 369.36, \"end\": 375.52, \"text\": \"But if you get caught, you could end up wearing a handcuff that literally chains you to the\"}, {\"start\": 375.52, \"end\": 377.76, \"text\": \"game.\"}, {\"start\": 377.76, \"end\": 381.92, \"text\": \"The cheaters edition is expected to be released this fall.\"}, {\"start\": 384.32, \"end\": 403.2, \"text\": \"Wendy's is going after McDonald's in a new Super Bowl ad for its so-called \\\"flash frozen\\\" burgers.\"}, {\"start\": 403.2, \"end\": 409.68, \"text\": \"A spokesperson for the fast food chain said\"}, {\"start\": 409.84, \"end\": 415.04, \"text\": \"\\\"this is the first time Wendy's has directly called out a competitor\\\" in a TV ad.\"}, {\"start\": 415.04, \"end\": 416.32, \"text\": \"Check it out.\"}, {\"start\": 448.08, \"end\": 451.52, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 451.52, \"end\": 453.04, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 453.04, \"end\": 455.48, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 455.48, \"end\": 460.64, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 460.68, \"end\": 466.84, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "wneZ68oct1U": {
    "video_id": "wneZ68oct1U",
    "title": "Dr. G answers your questions: Can babies and children die from coronavirus?",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200322",
    "duration": 44,
    "view_count": 262,
    "description": "Posted 3.22.20",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.34, \"end\": 7.68, \"text\": \"This question is from Jetsy Hoppenrath Sosa.\"}, {\"start\": 7.7, \"end\": 14.82, \"text\": \"She says I noticed lots of elders dying but I’m curious if any children, babies or adult\"}, {\"start\": 14.82, \"end\": 16.86, \"text\": \"die from it as well?\"}, {\"start\": 16.86, \"end\": 19.74, \"text\": \"Yes. It is serious\"}, {\"start\": 19.84, \"end\": 29.04, \"text\": \"Many people are dying but I want you to know that most people who get the virus will recover.\"}, {\"start\": 29.04, \"end\": 31.92, \"text\": \"But they can die.\"}, {\"start\": 31.93, \"end\": 34.62, \"text\": \"So you need to pay attention and take it seriously.\"}, {\"start\": 34.62, \"end\": 42.56, \"text\": \"I know staying home is hard but it will protect you and your family and other people as well.\"}]"
  },
  "U9n99OeLKG8": {
    "video_id": "U9n99OeLKG8",
    "title": "Deaf literacy bill passes in Georgia (ASL - 3.15.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180316",
    "duration": 83,
    "view_count": 124,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.94, \"end\": 5.74, \"text\": \"Big news for Georgia's deaf community.\"}, {\"start\": 5.74, \"end\": 15.38, \"text\": \"Today lawmakers passed House Bill 844 by a unanimous vote, 49-0.\"}, {\"start\": 15.38, \"end\": 25.4, \"text\": \"HB 844 is called \\\"Georgia Pathway.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 25.4, \"end\": 34.48, \"text\": \"The bill monitors the state's Deaf and hard of hearing children, their language acquisition,\"}, {\"start\": 34.48, \"end\": 38.24, \"text\": \"development and literacy.\"}, {\"start\": 38.36, \"end\": 45.32, \"text\": \"The bill involved three agencies who work with Deaf and hard of hearing children, plus\"}, {\"start\": 45.32, \"end\": 48.26, \"text\": \"other disabilities.\"}, {\"start\": 48.26, \"end\": 56.5, \"text\": \"They wanted to pool all of their resources so everyone was working towards the same goal,\"}, {\"start\": 56.5, \"end\": 61.94, \"text\": \"making sure no children fall through the cracks.\"}, {\"start\": 61.94, \"end\": 74.22, \"text\": \"Georgia representative Penny Houston and Senator P.K. Martin also provided support\"}, {\"start\": 74.22, \"end\": 77.12, \"text\": \"in passing the bill.\"}, {\"start\": 77.12, \"end\": 82.04, \"text\": \"Now the bill moves to the governor's office for the final approval.\"}]"
  },
  "MET7iOk_UCE": {
    "video_id": "MET7iOk_UCE",
    "title": "Super blue blood moon visible on January 31st (ASL - 1.20.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180120",
    "duration": 46,
    "view_count": 334,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.72, \"end\": 5.88, \"text\": \"You've heard of super moons, blue moons and blood moons.\"}, {\"start\": 5.88, \"end\": 15.18, \"text\": \"A \\\"supermoon\\\" occurs when the full moon is close to earth and brighter than normal.\"}, {\"start\": 15.18, \"end\": 26.06, \"text\": \"A \\\"blood moon\\\" occurs when it takes on a reddish tint as it passes through Earth's shadow in\"}, {\"start\": 26.1, \"end\": 27.58, \"text\": \"a lunar eclipse.\"}, {\"start\": 27.58, \"end\": 30.56, \"text\": \"A \\\"blue moon\\\" has nothing to do with color.\"}, {\"start\": 30.56, \"end\": 34.34, \"text\": \"It simply refers to the very unusual occurrence of two full moons in a single month.\"}, {\"start\": 34.34, \"end\": 41.38, \"text\": \"Depending on where you are on January 31st, you'll be able to see all three in one: a\"}, {\"start\": 41.38, \"end\": 44.8, \"text\": \"super blue blood moon.\"}]"
  },
  "g8T1bH8AOpg": {
    "video_id": "g8T1bH8AOpg",
    "title": "Maryland school shooter dead, 2 injured (ASL - 3.20.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180321",
    "duration": 75,
    "view_count": 181,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.96, \"end\": 14.46, \"text\": \"Just before 8 AM Tuesday morning, police say 17-year-old Austin Rollins shot a male and\"}, {\"start\": 14.46, \"end\": 18.44, \"text\": \"female student in the hallway at Great Mills high school in Maryland.\"}, {\"start\": 18.44, \"end\": 24.18, \"text\": \"Witnesses say the school's resource officer responded to the scene in less than one minute\"}, {\"start\": 24.18, \"end\": 26.58, \"text\": \"and he and Rollins simultaneously exchanged gunfire.\"}, {\"start\": 26.58, \"end\": 31.12, \"text\": \"Rollins was killed, the officer was unharmed.\"}, {\"start\": 31.12, \"end\": 38.14, \"text\": \"The 16-year-old female student Rollins shot is listed in critical condition and the 14-year-old\"}, {\"start\": 38.14, \"end\": 43.84, \"text\": \"male student is listed in stable condition.\"}, {\"start\": 43.84, \"end\": 49.32, \"text\": \"Authorities say Rollins was in a prior relationship with the female student but they are not sure\"}, {\"start\": 49.32, \"end\": 52.04, \"text\": \"if that factored into Rollins' motive for the shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 52.04, \"end\": 58.96, \"text\": \"Investigators are now collecting forensic evidence from multiple crime scenes and looking\"}, {\"start\": 58.96, \"end\": 65.5, \"text\": \"through electronic devices owned by Rollins.\"}, {\"start\": 65.5, \"end\": 73.92, \"text\": \"This is the 17th school shooting in the United States since January 1.\"}]"
  },
  "1gcINL-bie0": {
    "video_id": "1gcINL-bie0",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.17.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180118",
    "duration": 641,
    "view_count": 1388,
    "description": "1.17.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Government shutdown looms, GOP disagree on resolution \n-Flake criticizes Trump during Senate floor speech \n-Bannon strikes a deal \n-Former USA Gymnastics coach faces sexual abuse victims \n-Gymnast McKayla Maroney won't be fined $100k \n-Michigan father deported, hard to explain to kids \n-Meteor lights up Michigan sky \n-Starbucks has a secret Harry Potter menu \n\nSign1News is the first and on",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.42, \"end\": 7.28, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.28, \"end\": 9.16, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.16, \"end\": 10.2, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 10.2, \"end\": 13.12, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.88, \"end\": 22.36, \"text\": \"With every passing second, the deadline for a government shutdown gets closer.\"}, {\"start\": 22.36, \"end\": 29.4, \"text\": \"Lawmakers have until Friday to come up with some sort of resolution.\"}, {\"start\": 29.4, \"end\": 37.76, \"text\": \"And although Republicans are in charge of the House and the Senate, there is division\"}, {\"start\": 37.76, \"end\": 39.68, \"text\": \"within the party.\"}, {\"start\": 39.68, \"end\": 49.04, \"text\": \"On Tuesday, House Republican leaders offered a resolution which would delay a shut down\"}, {\"start\": 49.04, \"end\": 51.96, \"text\": \"until mid- February.\"}, {\"start\": 51.96, \"end\": 68.12, \"text\": \"But the House \\\"Freedom Caucus\\\", which is made up of conservative Republicans, says the party\"}, {\"start\": 68.12, \"end\": 71.44, \"text\": \"doesn't have enough votes to pass the plan.\"}, {\"start\": 71.44, \"end\": 80.56, \"text\": \"And Democrats say they won't agree on any spending bill until a deal is set for the\"}, {\"start\": 80.56, \"end\": 87.84, \"text\": \"DACA program, which expires on March 5th.\"}, {\"start\": 90.8, \"end\": 102.68, \"text\": \"Republican Senator Jeff Flake delivered a powerful Senate floor speech Wednesday morning,\"}, {\"start\": 102.68, \"end\": 115.28, \"text\": \"slamming President Trump's attacks on the news media.\"}, {\"start\": 115.28, \"end\": 125.0, \"text\": \"Flake criticized the president for calling the news media the \\\"enemy of the people\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 125.0, \"end\": 133.12, \"text\": \"and for repeatedly accusing them of reporting \\\"fake news.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 133.12, \"end\": 148.4, \"text\": \"He says a president that can't take criticism is charting a dangerous path.\"}, {\"start\": 148.4, \"end\": 155.44, \"text\": \"And he criticized his fellow lawmakers who have sat back quietly and said nothing.\"}, {\"start\": 155.44, \"end\": 164.68, \"text\": \"Flake's been a frequent and vocal Trump critic.\"}, {\"start\": 164.68, \"end\": 171.36, \"text\": \"He has announced that he will not be seeking reelection this year and he said he will use\"}, {\"start\": 171.36, \"end\": 178.68, \"text\": \"his remaining Senate time to speak out against Trump whenever it's warranted.\"}, {\"start\": 182.2, \"end\": 189.8, \"text\": \"Former White House chief strategist Steve Bannon has struck a deal with special counsel\"}, {\"start\": 189.8, \"end\": 202.72, \"text\": \"Robert Mueller's team to be interviewed by prosecutors -- instead of testifying before\"}, {\"start\": 202.72, \"end\": 208.52, \"text\": \"a grand jury.\"}, {\"start\": 208.52, \"end\": 212.4, \"text\": \"Two sources told CNN Bannon is expected to cooperate and talk openly with Mueller's team\"}, {\"start\": 212.4, \"end\": 217.08, \"text\": \"about the Russia investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 217.08, \"end\": 220.64, \"text\": \"The sources did not say when the interview will take place.\"}, {\"start\": 220.64, \"end\": 230.08, \"text\": \"A spokesman for the special counsel's office declined to comment.\"}, {\"start\": 233.28, \"end\": 242.0, \"text\": \"For a second day, former USA gymnastics doctor Larry Nassar appeared in a Michigan courtroom\"}, {\"start\": 242.0, \"end\": 249.04, \"text\": \"to face the victims he sexually abused for nearly 20 years.\"}, {\"start\": 249.04, \"end\": 255.36, \"text\": \"More than 140 female athletes have accused Nassar of sexually abusing them.\"}, {\"start\": 255.36, \"end\": 266.36, \"text\": \"He pleaded guilty in November to seven counts of criminal sexual assault.\"}, {\"start\": 266.36, \"end\": 276.2, \"text\": \"Over 80 women and their parents are expected to give graphic victim impact statements at\"}, {\"start\": 276.2, \"end\": 278.04, \"text\": \"his sentencing this week.\"}, {\"start\": 278.04, \"end\": 286.16, \"text\": \"During yesterday's statements, Nassar sat with his head down refusing to look up at\"}, {\"start\": 286.16, \"end\": 290.2, \"text\": \"his victims.\"}, {\"start\": 292.6, \"end\": 302.08, \"text\": \"Olympic gold medalist McKayla Maroney was one of the 140 women to accuse team USA doctor\"}, {\"start\": 302.08, \"end\": 309.76, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar of sexually abusing her.\"}, {\"start\": 309.76, \"end\": 317.88, \"text\": \"But Maroney signed a non-disclosure agreement as part of a settlement with USA Gymnastics.\"}, {\"start\": 317.88, \"end\": 327.6, \"text\": \"The agreement said if she publicly talked to anyone about the abuse she would be fine\"}, {\"start\": 327.6, \"end\": 330.08, \"text\": \"$100,000.\"}, {\"start\": 330.08, \"end\": 339.32, \"text\": \"Now officials with USA Gymnastics say she will not be fine if she speaks out or shares\"}, {\"start\": 339.32, \"end\": 346.52, \"text\": \"her story regarding her abuse at the hands of Nassar.\"}, {\"start\": 350.44, \"end\": 365.8, \"text\": \"Thirty-nine-year-old Jose Garcia said a painful goodbye to his family in Detroit on Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 365.8, \"end\": 369.76, \"text\": \"Garcia has lived in the United States for 30 years.\"}, {\"start\": 369.76, \"end\": 374.48, \"text\": \"He has two children and no criminal record.\"}, {\"start\": 374.48, \"end\": 377.36, \"text\": \"But now he is being deported to Mexico.\"}, {\"start\": 377.36, \"end\": 387.68, \"text\": \"He came to the country with his parents who were undocumented immigrants.\"}, {\"start\": 387.68, \"end\": 392.96, \"text\": \"Garcia is considered a \\\"dreamer.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 392.96, \"end\": 401.6, \"text\": \"Officials with Immigration and Customs Enforcement say Garcia had to leave the country because\"}, {\"start\": 401.6, \"end\": 407.04, \"text\": \"there was no DACA law currently in place.\"}, {\"start\": 407.04, \"end\": 413.36, \"text\": \"Garcia had been facing deportation since 2009 but had received extensions under the Obama\"}, {\"start\": 413.36, \"end\": 416.08, \"text\": \"administration.\"}, {\"start\": 416.08, \"end\": 428.64, \"text\": \"Because of the Trump administration's crackdown on undocumented immigrants, Garcia was ordered\"}, {\"start\": 428.96, \"end\": 431.84, \"text\": \"to return to Mexico.\"}, {\"start\": 431.84, \"end\": 441.92, \"text\": \"He says before he left, his son wouldn't talk and all his daughter could do was cry.\"}, {\"start\": 444.8, \"end\": 453.36, \"text\": \"A massive ball of fire was spotted streaking across the night sky in Michigan Tuesday night.\"}, {\"start\": 453.44, \"end\": 456.32, \"text\": \"Eyewitnesses say the flash was also accompanied by a loud boom.\"}, {\"start\": 456.32, \"end\": 467.2, \"text\": \"It was caught on dashcam and surveillance cameras across the state.\"}, {\"start\": 467.2, \"end\": 469.12, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 499.52, \"end\": 508.36, \"text\": \"Some social media reports say the flash was seen as far away as Chicago.\"}, {\"start\": 508.36, \"end\": 517.8, \"text\": \"The National Weather Service says it was likely a meteor and that it caused a magnitude 2.0\"}, {\"start\": 517.8, \"end\": 519.76, \"text\": \"earthquake.\"}, {\"start\": 519.76, \"end\": 527.2, \"text\": \"According to the US Geological Survey, the earthquake was centered about 40 miles northeast\"}, {\"start\": 527.2, \"end\": 531.36, \"text\": \"of Detroit.\"}, {\"start\": 534.08, \"end\": 546.56, \"text\": \"Starbucks reportedly has a secret menu with three drinks inspired by Harry Potter books\"}, {\"start\": 546.56, \"end\": 548.4, \"text\": \"and films.\"}, {\"start\": 548.4, \"end\": 564.64, \"text\": \"According to the unofficial Starbucks secret menu site, they are: butterbeer latte, butterbeer\"}, {\"start\": 564.64, \"end\": 571.52, \"text\": \"frappuccino and Harry Potter's pumpkin juice.\"}, {\"start\": 571.52, \"end\": 576.96, \"text\": \"But here's the thing: you just can't go in and ask for them by name.\"}, {\"start\": 576.96, \"end\": 579.84, \"text\": \"You have to know how to order them.\"}, {\"start\": 579.84, \"end\": 599.68, \"text\": \"For example: to get a butterbeer frappuccino, ask for a creme frappuccino with three pumps\"}, {\"start\": 599.68, \"end\": 608.32, \"text\": \"each of carmel and toffee nut syrups and carmel drizzle on top.\"}, {\"start\": 608.32, \"end\": 616.32, \"text\": \"Check the Starbucks secret menu site for the rest of the recipes.\"}, {\"start\": 619.04, \"end\": 621.44, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 621.44, \"end\": 622.64, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 622.72, \"end\": 624.8, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 624.8, \"end\": 629.12, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 629.12, \"end\": 633.8, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "G6bZDfnv0Hc": {
    "video_id": "G6bZDfnv0Hc",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.27.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171128",
    "duration": 576,
    "view_count": 575,
    "description": "November 27, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-PRINCE HARRY, MEGHAN MARKLE ENGAGEMENT\n-LAWSUIT CHALLENGES TRUMP'S PICK TO LEAD CFPB\n-OFFICER SHOOTS MALL THEFT SUSPECT\n-MOUNT AGUNG VOLCANO EVACUATIONS\n-MYANMAR WELCOMES THE POPE\n-MELANIA TRUMP DECORATES WHITE HOUSE\n-MISS UNIVERSE 2017\n-DICTIONARY.COM WORD OF THE YEAR\n-COP'S NINJA MOVE SAVES HIM FROM ONCOMING CAR\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.27, \"end\": 7.48, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.48, \"end\": 8.48, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.48, \"end\": 9.88, \"text\": \"I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 9.88, \"end\": 14.3, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.3, \"end\": 17.29, \"text\": \"Happy news from London today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.29, \"end\": 21.28, \"text\": \"Prince Harry is engaged.\"}, {\"start\": 21.3, \"end\": 32.46, \"text\": \"According to the royal family Prince Harry quietly became engaged to\"}, {\"start\": 32.48, \"end\": 37.5, \"text\": \"American actress Meghan Markle.\"}, {\"start\": 37.5, \"end\": 47.1, \"text\": \"They made their debut as an engaged couple at Kensington Palace after the announcement.\"}, {\"start\": 47.11, \"end\": 55.07, \"text\": \"Markle said the couple was introduced by a friend.\"}, {\"start\": 55.07, \"end\": 62.5, \"text\": \"Prince Harry said he knew she was \\\"The One\\\" the first time they met.\"}, {\"start\": 62.5, \"end\": 66.24, \"text\": \"The wedding will take place next spring.\"}, {\"start\": 67.96, \"end\": 78.88, \"text\": \"President Trump is now facing a legal battle over who will head the Consumer Financial\"}, {\"start\": 78.94, \"end\": 89.64, \"text\": \"Protection Bureau or CFPB.\"}, {\"start\": 89.7, \"end\": 98.18, \"text\": \"Leandra English has filed a lawsuit to stop the president\"}, {\"start\": 98.18, \"end\": 107.0, \"text\": \"from installing his budget director as head of CFPB.\"}, {\"start\": 107.02, \"end\": 117.34, \"text\": \"The lawsuit is seeking legal clarity on succession protocol within the agency.\"}, {\"start\": 117.34, \"end\": 127.68, \"text\": \"Today Mick Mulvaney showed up for work at the agency\"}, {\"start\": 127.68, \"end\": 131.02, \"text\": \"to take charge as the interim director\"}, {\"start\": 131.04, \"end\": 140.48, \"text\": \"and told staffers to disregard any instructions they get from English.\"}, {\"start\": 142.78, \"end\": 150.18, \"text\": \"A police officer in Texas shoots a robbery suspect who pointed a fake gun.\"}, {\"start\": 150.22, \"end\": 157.1, \"text\": \"According to the Arlington Police Department officers responded to a call about a shoplifter\"}, {\"start\": 157.1, \"end\": 159.34, \"text\": \"at the Parks Mall Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 159.4, \"end\": 165.74, \"text\": \"Once police spotted the suspect, a chase began.\"}, {\"start\": 165.74, \"end\": 172.14, \"text\": \"The suspect then pulled what looked like a weapon from his waistband\"}, {\"start\": 172.14, \"end\": 174.16, \"text\": \"and held it toward an officer.\"}, {\"start\": 174.24, \"end\": 176.7, \"text\": \"That what caused the officer to open fire.\"}, {\"start\": 176.7, \"end\": 182.72, \"text\": \"It was later discovered the weapon was a BB gun.\"}, {\"start\": 182.74, \"end\": 189.84, \"text\": \"The suspect was taken to a local hospital for treatment.\"}, {\"start\": 189.94, \"end\": 193.76, \"text\": \"No one else was injured in the incident.\"}, {\"start\": 195.94, \"end\": 207.74, \"text\": \"Authorities in Indonesia have issued the highest level warning possible after volcanic eruptions\"}, {\"start\": 207.76, \"end\": 211.24, \"text\": \"from Mount Agung -- level 4.\"}, {\"start\": 211.24, \"end\": 217.34, \"text\": \"The volcano is located on the island of Bali.\"}, {\"start\": 217.44, \"end\": 221.32, \"text\": \"The eruptions have forced the closure of the island's main airport\"}, {\"start\": 221.32, \"end\": 227.7, \"text\": \"and evacuation of thousands of residents living nearby.\"}, {\"start\": 227.7, \"end\": 234.0, \"text\": \"There were multiple volcanic blasts this weekend\"}, {\"start\": 234.0, \"end\": 240.08, \"text\": \"which spewed smoke and ash thousands of meters into the air.\"}, {\"start\": 240.12, \"end\": 248.68, \"text\": \"Level 4 means there is the potential for another larger eruption.\"}, {\"start\": 248.68, \"end\": 257.8, \"text\": \"Authorities have ordered anyone within a 6 mile radius of the peak to evacuate.\"}, {\"start\": 259.96, \"end\": 267.16, \"text\": \"Pope Francis is visiting Myanmar --\"}, {\"start\": 267.16, \"end\": 270.96, \"text\": \"making him the first pope to ever visit the Southeast nation.\"}, {\"start\": 271.04, \"end\": 275.16, \"text\": \"His visit comes as the staunchly Buddhist country is accused of horrifying acts of brutality\"}, {\"start\": 275.16, \"end\": 290.08, \"text\": \"against its Rohingya Muslim minority.\"}, {\"start\": 290.12, \"end\": 299.8, \"text\": \"The Pope has publicly decried violence against the Rohingya,\"}, {\"start\": 299.8, \"end\": 305.24, \"text\": \"calling them \\\"persecuted brothers and sisters.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 305.28, \"end\": 313.24, \"text\": \"He met with Myanmar's military leader for about 15 minutes.\"}, {\"start\": 313.24, \"end\": 317.8, \"text\": \"The specifics of the meeting were not disclosed\"}, {\"start\": 317.8, \"end\": 325.12, \"text\": \"but many are hoping the conversation will lead the country down a path of peace.\"}, {\"start\": 327.48, \"end\": 329.68, \"text\": \"Take a look at this.\"}, {\"start\": 329.68, \"end\": 333.68, \"text\": \"It's this year's holiday decor at the White House.\"}, {\"start\": 333.76, \"end\": 348.56, \"text\": \"First lady Melania Trump unveiled this year's holiday theme: \\\"Time Honored Traditions.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 348.64, \"end\": 358.32, \"text\": \"The White House says the First Lady personally selected every detail of\"}, {\"start\": 358.32, \"end\": 366.56, \"text\": \"And she had a good deal of help -- with about 150 volunteers from 29 states spending more\"}, {\"start\": 366.56, \"end\": 374.24, \"text\": \"than 1600 hours decorating over the Thanksgiving holiday.\"}, {\"start\": 374.24, \"end\": 378.76, \"text\": \"And there's plenty of holiday items to put up --\"}, {\"start\": 378.76, \"end\": 381.44, \"text\": \"more than 12,000 ornaments\"}, {\"start\": 381.44, \"end\": 385.68, \"text\": \"and 18,000 feet of strung lights for starters.\"}, {\"start\": 385.68, \"end\": 389.4, \"text\": \"Then there is the official White House Christmas tree --\"}, {\"start\": 389.4, \"end\": 400.44, \"text\": \"an 18-foot tall balsam is now set up in the White House blue room.\"}, {\"start\": 402.6, \"end\": 410.88, \"text\": \"Congratulations to 22-year-old Demi-Leigh Nel-Peters of South Africa.\"}, {\"start\": 410.96, \"end\": 418.24, \"text\": \"She was crowned Miss Universe last night in Las Vegas.\"}, {\"start\": 418.32, \"end\": 422.36, \"text\": \"She is the second woman South Africa to earn the crown.\"}, {\"start\": 422.44, \"end\": 430.84, \"text\": \"She says she wants to use her reign to champion HIV/AIDS and self-defense causes.\"}, {\"start\": 430.84, \"end\": 444.12, \"text\": \"In addition to the crown, Nel-Peters gets a year-long salary, a luxury apartment in\"}, {\"start\": 444.2, \"end\": 447.32, \"text\": \"New York City and a host of prizes.\"}, {\"start\": 449.6, \"end\": 456.88, \"text\": \"Dictionary.com has revealed its word of the year for 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 456.88, \"end\": 459.48, \"text\": \"And here it is.\"}, {\"start\": 459.6, \"end\": 463.16, \"text\": \"The word is complicit.\"}, {\"start\": 463.16, \"end\": 472.16, \"text\": \"It means choosing to be involved in an illegal or questionable acts and\"}, {\"start\": 472.16, \"end\": 477.72, \"text\": \"having partnership involvement in wrongdoing.\"}, {\"start\": 477.72, \"end\": 486.32, \"text\": \"Interest in the word spiked in March when Saturday Night Live aired a fake commercial\"}, {\"start\": 486.32, \"end\": 489.4, \"text\": \"for \\\"Complicit\\\" perfume.\"}, {\"start\": 489.44, \"end\": 497.72, \"text\": \"A month later, President Trump's daughter, Ivanka, told CBS that she didn't even know\"}, {\"start\": 497.8, \"end\": 502.68, \"text\": \"what it meant to be complicit.\"}, {\"start\": 502.68, \"end\": 511.76, \"text\": \"And complicit has also come up in the wake of allegations of sexual misconduct by Hollywood\"}, {\"start\": 511.76, \"end\": 520.08, \"text\": \"mogul Harvey Weinstein and other powerful men.\"}, {\"start\": 522.32, \"end\": 525.68, \"text\": \"And check out this video.\"}, {\"start\": 525.72, \"end\": 530.08, \"text\": \"It shows a New Jersey cop doing some impressive ninja moves.\"}, {\"start\": 530.08, \"end\": 538.76, \"text\": \"The officer was on the side of the road, investigating a car accident, when another vehicle sped\"}, {\"start\": 538.76, \"end\": 541.36, \"text\": \"by nearly striking the officer.\"}, {\"start\": 541.36, \"end\": 549.08, \"text\": \"The officer was able to avoid the accident with a nifty cop-drop-and-roll move.\"}, {\"start\": 549.16, \"end\": 553.28, \"text\": \"The car was later pulled over and the drivers issued a citation.\"}, {\"start\": 555.32, \"end\": 556.72, \"text\": \"And those you top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 556.72, \"end\": 557.76, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 557.76, \"end\": 559.88, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 560.08, \"end\": 564.12, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 564.12, \"end\": 569.2, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "obI6De8I_0M": {
    "video_id": "obI6De8I_0M",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.7.2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171208",
    "duration": 622,
    "view_count": 520,
    "description": "December 7, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-AL FRANKEN RESIGNS\n-SEXUAL HARASSMENT HEARING ON CAPITOL HILL\n-WINDS FUELING CALIFORNIA WILDFIRES\n-PROTESTS AGAINST TRUMP'S JERUSALEM DECISION\n-EX-POLICE OFFICER SENTENCED TO 20 YEARS FOR MURDER\n-TAMPA MURDER SUSPECT'S PARENTS IN COURT\n-INJURED DOG GETS 3-D PRINTED MASK\n-STARBUCKS DEBUTS CHRISTMAS TREE FRAPPUCCINO\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day t",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.44, \"end\": 11.42, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.48, \"end\": 12.7, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.74, \"end\": 15.02, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.6, \"end\": 22.22, \"text\": \"Today Democratic Senator Al Franken announced he is stepping down.\"}, {\"start\": 22.24, \"end\": 26.56, \"text\": \"He is resigning after being accused of touching several women inappropriately.\"}, {\"start\": 26.58, \"end\": 34.9, \"text\": \"On Wednesday more than 30 Democratic senators called on Franken to step aside.\"}, {\"start\": 34.96, \"end\": 42.58, \"text\": \"The Senate ethics committee began investigating Franken in November after a radio anchor\"}, {\"start\": 42.58, \"end\": 52.64, \"text\": \"accused him of groping and forcibly kissing her during the 2006 USO tour.\"}, {\"start\": 52.7, \"end\": 57.32, \"text\": \"While Franken is stepping down, he stopped short of apologizing.\"}, {\"start\": 57.36, \"end\": 62.08, \"text\": \"He says some of the allegations are simply not true\"}, {\"start\": 62.18, \"end\": 66.06, \"text\": \"and the other allegations he remembers differently\"}, {\"start\": 66.06, \"end\": 68.86, \"text\": \"than what the women are reporting.\"}, {\"start\": 70.34, \"end\": 78.78, \"text\": \"Members of the House Administration Committee met Thursday on Capitol Hill to examine how\"}, {\"start\": 78.78, \"end\": 84.72, \"text\": \"sexual harassment complaints are handled in Congress.\"}, {\"start\": 84.78, \"end\": 89.28, \"text\": \"It's the committee second meeting in less than a month.\"}, {\"start\": 89.3, \"end\": 98.68, \"text\": \"There is broad agreement that the current system doesn't work and that reforms are needed,\"}, {\"start\": 98.68, \"end\": 101.5, \"text\": \"but there's not yet been agreement on what to do about it.\"}, {\"start\": 101.52, \"end\": 107.22, \"text\": \"There have been numerous calls for a complete overhaul of the system to bring more accountability.\"}, {\"start\": 107.3, \"end\": 119.92, \"text\": \"Among the reform proposals -- a bipartisan bill to eliminate a US Treasury fund used\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 124.08, \"text\": \"to pay out sexual harassment settlements.\"}, {\"start\": 125.9, \"end\": 132.14, \"text\": \"The fires in Southern California are so big\"}, {\"start\": 132.14, \"end\": 136.54, \"text\": \"smoke can be seen from the International Space Station.\"}, {\"start\": 136.6, \"end\": 139.66, \"text\": \"And the situation is likely to get worse.\"}, {\"start\": 139.68, \"end\": 148.08, \"text\": \"Strong winds and dry weather are causing the flames to spread quickly.\"}, {\"start\": 148.1, \"end\": 154.58, \"text\": \"Fire crews are having a hard time slowing down the spread.\"}, {\"start\": 154.6, \"end\": 160.92, \"text\": \"About 5,000 firefighters are battling the fires.\"}, {\"start\": 160.92, \"end\": 173.62, \"text\": \"The four biggest fires have consumed about 116,000 acres\"}, {\"start\": 173.62, \"end\": 180.34, \"text\": \"and force more than 100,000 people from their homes.\"}, {\"start\": 180.34, \"end\": 189.48, \"text\": \"More than 260 public and charter schools in the Los Angeles area are closed throughout\"}, {\"start\": 189.48, \"end\": 192.08, \"text\": \"the rest of the week.\"}, {\"start\": 192.16, \"end\": 206.68, \"text\": \"And health officials advise residents to limit their outdoor time because of the smoke.\"}, {\"start\": 206.68, \"end\": 213.4, \"text\": \"The situation is so bad that fire officials have created a new category -- \\\"Purple\\\" -- for\"}, {\"start\": 213.4, \"end\": 223.86, \"text\": \"the color-coded fire danger system.\"}, {\"start\": 223.9, \"end\": 233.38, \"text\": \"Officials say a score of 48 is considered high danger and 163 is extreme.\"}, {\"start\": 233.42, \"end\": 237.1, \"text\": \"Thursday's score was a record-setting 296.\"}, {\"start\": 239.08, \"end\": 250.24, \"text\": \"President Trump's decision to recognize Jerusalem as the capital of Israel has sparked protests.\"}, {\"start\": 250.25, \"end\": 263.34, \"text\": \"This was the scene Thursday in the West Bank city of Ramallah.\"}, {\"start\": 263.34, \"end\": 278.16, \"text\": \"You can see fires burning in the street and people throwing rocks, tires and other objects.\"}, {\"start\": 278.16, \"end\": 289.7, \"text\": \"Trump's decision has angered many across the world, particularly Palestinian leaders who\"}, {\"start\": 289.74, \"end\": 302.08, \"text\": \"say Trump's move disqualifies the U.S. from mediating peace talks\"}, {\"start\": 302.08, \"end\": 306.96, \"text\": \"between Israel and the Palestinians.\"}, {\"start\": 307.02, \"end\": 314.12, \"text\": \"Trump says he remains committed to finding a permanent peace in the Middle East.\"}, {\"start\": 316.4, \"end\": 325.34, \"text\": \"Former South Carolina police officer Michael Slager has been sentenced to 20 years\"}, {\"start\": 325.34, \"end\": 329.18, \"text\": \"in federal prison for murder.\"}, {\"start\": 329.2, \"end\": 341.12, \"text\": \"In 2015 Slager killed unarmed black man Walter Scott.\"}, {\"start\": 341.24, \"end\": 351.48, \"text\": \"Take a look -- this is video of the shooting captured on someone's cell phone.\"}, {\"start\": 351.5, \"end\": 358.2, \"text\": \"Scott had been pulled over for a broken tail light on his car.\"}, {\"start\": 358.2, \"end\": 365.86, \"text\": \"Slager shot Scott in the back five times as he was running away.\"}, {\"start\": 365.98, \"end\": 370.98, \"text\": \"Scott's family believes he ran because he thought he was being arrested\"}, {\"start\": 370.98, \"end\": 373.9, \"text\": \"over back child support.\"}, {\"start\": 373.96, \"end\": 379.94, \"text\": \"Federal prosecutors were seeking a life sentence in prison.\"}, {\"start\": 379.98, \"end\": 384.06, \"text\": \"But the judge in the case decided on 20 years.\"}, {\"start\": 385.98, \"end\": 394.64, \"text\": \"Last week Tampa police arrested Howell Donaldson III, charging him in the deaths of four people\"}, {\"start\": 394.64, \"end\": 404.42, \"text\": \"in the Seminole Heights neighborhood.\"}, {\"start\": 404.44, \"end\": 411.52, \"text\": \"Today Donaldson's parents were in court to explain why\"}, {\"start\": 411.52, \"end\": 413.8, \"text\": \"they are not cooperating with authorities.\"}, {\"start\": 413.8, \"end\": 418.52, \"text\": \"Prosecutors say the parents refused to answer questions\"}, {\"start\": 418.52, \"end\": 426.94, \"text\": \"during a meeting with investigators earlier this week.\"}, {\"start\": 426.96, \"end\": 436.86, \"text\": \"Prosecutors say Donaldson's parents are committing contempt by not cooperating.\"}, {\"start\": 436.86, \"end\": 444.68, \"text\": \"But the parents' lawyer says investigators are trying to divide the family by forcing\"}, {\"start\": 444.68, \"end\": 449.72, \"text\": \"the parents to testify against their son.\"}, {\"start\": 449.72, \"end\": 456.66, \"text\": \"A judge will decide whether a hearing will be held on the matter.\"}, {\"start\": 458.88, \"end\": 469.42, \"text\": \"Thanks to doctors at University of California-Davis and a special 3-D printed mask,\"}, {\"start\": 469.42, \"end\": 473.76, \"text\": \"an injured dog is on the mend.\"}, {\"start\": 473.76, \"end\": 481.68, \"text\": \"\\\"Loca\\\" had been attacked by another dog and suffered severe trauma to her skull.\"}, {\"start\": 481.68, \"end\": 489.58, \"text\": \"While the medical staff treated the dog's injuries, students printed an exoskeleton\"}, {\"start\": 489.58, \"end\": 498.78, \"text\": \"mask based on a CT scan of her head.\"}, {\"start\": 498.82, \"end\": 511.22, \"text\": \"It was a joint effort between oral surgeons and biomedical engineering staff.\"}, {\"start\": 511.26, \"end\": 521.62, \"text\": \"Loca was the first patient to try out the mask, which stabilize the injury like a cast.\"}, {\"start\": 521.62, \"end\": 528.28, \"text\": \"Months after the surgery, doctors say Loca is doing well.\"}, {\"start\": 529.64, \"end\": 540.48, \"text\": \"Starbucks wants to help get coffee lovers get in the holiday spirit.\"}, {\"start\": 540.48, \"end\": 549.48, \"text\": \"For a very limited time the company is offering its new Christmas tree frappaccino.\"}, {\"start\": 549.6, \"end\": 557.64, \"text\": \"It's available through Monday at participating locations in the US and Canada.\"}, {\"start\": 557.64, \"end\": 574.04, \"text\": \"The drink is a peppermint mocha creme frappaccino topped with green matcha whipped cream.\"}, {\"start\": 574.08, \"end\": 583.84, \"text\": \"It is adorned with caramel drizzle, representing a garland, and cranberries made to look like\"}, {\"start\": 583.84, \"end\": 589.96, \"text\": \"ornaments -- then topped off with a strawberry.\"}, {\"start\": 589.96, \"end\": 593.04, \"text\": \"The drink is made to look like a Christmas tree.\"}, {\"start\": 593.04, \"end\": 596.32, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 596.32, \"end\": 598.32, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 598.32, \"end\": 601.2, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 601.2, \"end\": 606.56, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 606.56, \"end\": 613.76, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "0VQ9H3AxdGc": {
    "video_id": "0VQ9H3AxdGc",
    "title": "Sign1News 8 7 20",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200807",
    "duration": 993,
    "view_count": 1550,
    "description": "Sign1News, a leading deaf news source, uses American Sign Language to cover the top news stories of the week about COVID-19 death toll forecast, students going back to school, and Instagram Reels.\n\nToday's Headlines\n-Grim new Covid forecast: Nearly 300,000 dead in US by December\n-Student suspended for posting picture of crowded hall\n-Stimulus deal in limbo, deadline nears\n-Volunteers clean up, rage grows in Beirut\n-Instagram's TikTok copycat 'Reels' is now available\n-'Dirty Dancing' sequel with ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.72, \"end\": 8.82, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.82, \"end\": 12.14, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 12.14, \"end\": 13.32, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.32, \"end\": 17.6, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 25.78, \"end\": 35.82, \"text\": \"The nationwide coronavirus death toll surpassed 160,000 overnight.\"}, {\"start\": 35.82, \"end\": 43.32, \"text\": \"And now a new model from the University of Washington offers a grim forecast.\"}, {\"start\": 43.32, \"end\": 52.82, \"text\": \"It predicts US deaths from coronavirus could hit nearly 300,000 by December.\"}, {\"start\": 52.82, \"end\": 64.44, \"text\": \"This all comes as numerous big cities are seeing a troubling spike in coronavirus cases.\"}, {\"start\": 64.44, \"end\": 76.22, \"text\": \"Before Ohio Governor Mike DeWine could greet President Trump on the tarmac just before\"}, {\"start\": 76.22, \"end\": 87.92, \"text\": \"a factory tour, he became one of the latest Americans to test positive for the coronavirus.\"}, {\"start\": 87.92, \"end\": 99.6, \"text\": \"DeWine said he had no symptoms and no reason to think he had Covid-19.\"}, {\"start\": 99.6, \"end\": 105.6, \"text\": \"He later tweeted that a second test was negative.\"}, {\"start\": 105.6, \"end\": 110.88, \"text\": \"However out of an abundance of caution and at the direction of medical professionals,\"}, {\"start\": 110.88, \"end\": 117.28, \"text\": \"DeWine and his wife will be taking another test on Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 117.28, \"end\": 126.36, \"text\": \"Meanwhile nine US cities and California's Central Valley are drawing concern.\"}, {\"start\": 126.36, \"end\": 141.2, \"text\": \"Dr. Deborah Birx warns of places like Kansas City seeing higher test positivity rates.\"}, {\"start\": 141.2, \"end\": 145.84, \"text\": \"Chicago also made the list.\"}, {\"start\": 145.84, \"end\": 161.4, \"text\": \"Illinois had its highest single day report since May 24, adding nearly 2,000 new cases Thursday.\"}, {\"start\": 161.4, \"end\": 171.84, \"text\": \"In Texas the Department of Health Services reported a 17% positivity rate even with the\"}, {\"start\": 171.84, \"end\": 183.12, \"text\": \"decline in hospitalizations for the third day in a row and a two day drop in new cases.\"}, {\"start\": 183.12, \"end\": 190.84, \"text\": \"In Tampa, Florida Hillsborough County Public schools announced it will begin the school\"}, {\"start\": 190.84, \"end\": 200.36, \"text\": \"year virtually despite Governor Ron DeSantis pushing for students to be back in the classroom\"}, {\"start\": 200.36, \"end\": 205.48, \"text\": \"and even participate in high school sports.\"}, {\"start\": 205.48, \"end\": 212.2, \"text\": \"There is one glimmer of hope.\"}, {\"start\": 212.2, \"end\": 219.92, \"text\": \"Even though the updated model projects the US death toll could reach nearly 300,000 by\"}, {\"start\": 219.92, \"end\": 233.8, \"text\": \"December 1, it also indicates about 70,000 lives could be saved if more people consistently wear masks.\"}, {\"start\": 236.32, \"end\": 245.76, \"text\": \"Hannah Watters, a Georgia high school student, says she was suspended after she posted this\"}, {\"start\": 245.76, \"end\": 253.88, \"text\": \"photo of a crowded high school hallway on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 253.88, \"end\": 263.6, \"text\": \"Watters is a sophomore at North Paulding high school in Dallas, Georgia.\"}, {\"start\": 263.6, \"end\": 271.24, \"text\": \"The 15-year-old posted on Twitter a photo showing students walking down a crowded hallway,\"}, {\"start\": 271.24, \"end\": 276.2, \"text\": \"some wearing masks, others without face coverings.\"}, {\"start\": 276.2, \"end\": 285.72, \"text\": \"Watters says she was accused of breaking several codes of conduct and suspended.\"}, {\"start\": 285.72, \"end\": 294.08, \"text\": \"But she said she did it because she was nervous and concerned.\"}, {\"start\": 294.08, \"end\": 303.4, \"text\": \"In a letter to the community Paulding County school Superintendent Brian Otott said the\"}, {\"start\": 303.4, \"end\": 309.38, \"text\": \"photo was taken out of context.\"}, {\"start\": 309.38, \"end\": 316.78, \"text\": \"The letter said \\\"class changes at the high school level are a challenge when maintaining\"}, {\"start\": 316.78, \"end\": 319.54, \"text\": \"a specific schedule.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 319.54, \"end\": 327.699, \"text\": \"He adds \\\"students are in this hallway environment for just a brief period as they moved to their\"}, {\"start\": 327.7, \"end\": 330.5, \"text\": \"next class.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 330.5, \"end\": 339.58, \"text\": \"After the story went viral, the superintendent changed his mind and reversed Watters' suspension.\"}, {\"start\": 339.58, \"end\": 346.44, \"text\": \"But it seems Watters is not the only person with concerns.\"}, {\"start\": 346.44, \"end\": 350.52, \"text\": \"[car horns blaring] This is video of dozens of teachers gathered outside the Gwinnett\"}, {\"start\": 350.52, \"end\": 358.62, \"text\": \"County school administrative building honking their horns in protest over the reopening\"}, {\"start\": 358.62, \"end\": 363.44, \"text\": \"of in-person schools.\"}, {\"start\": 368.2, \"end\": 376.38, \"text\": \"While the pandemic surges, talks between the White House and Democrats over the next round\"}, {\"start\": 376.38, \"end\": 381.84, \"text\": \"of economic stimulus are on the brink of collapse.\"}, {\"start\": 381.84, \"end\": 389.94, \"text\": \"Congress' self-imposed deadline for a stimulus deal is today (Friday).\"}, {\"start\": 389.94, \"end\": 401.14, \"text\": \"But it appears there is little chance of a bipartisan agreement before the weekend begins.\"}, {\"start\": 401.14, \"end\": 410.8, \"text\": \"Talks about the stimulus are in a stalemate.\"}, {\"start\": 410.8, \"end\": 420.6, \"text\": \"Top White House negotiators say big roadblocks remain after Thursday's three hour meeting\"}, {\"start\": 420.6, \"end\": 424.68, \"text\": \"with Democratic leaders.\"}, {\"start\": 424.68, \"end\": 432.7, \"text\": \"The White House Chief of Staff says both sides are willing to stay engaged in negotiations\"}, {\"start\": 432.7, \"end\": 443.32, \"text\": \"but their differences are significant.\"}, {\"start\": 443.32, \"end\": 453.28, \"text\": \"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi is disappointed with discussions, saying President Trump and\"}, {\"start\": 453.28, \"end\": 459.68, \"text\": \"Republicans do not understand the gravity of the situation.\"}, {\"start\": 459.68, \"end\": 467.84, \"text\": \"The points of disagreement haven't changed much since the sit-downs began.\"}, {\"start\": 467.84, \"end\": 479.36, \"text\": \"Republicans want to pass a 'skinny deal' that deals with some of the pressing issues but\"}, {\"start\": 479.36, \"end\": 488.8, \"text\": \"Democrats want to do something big just like with every other bill.\"}, {\"start\": 488.8, \"end\": 500.68, \"text\": \"White House administration officials say Trump may take executive action if the deal is not\"}, {\"start\": 500.68, \"end\": 505.22, \"text\": \"completed by today (Friday).\"}, {\"start\": 506.76, \"end\": 516.54, \"text\": \"Three days after Beirut's deadly explosion devastated Lebanon's capital, teams are searching\"}, {\"start\": 516.54, \"end\": 521.14, \"text\": \"for survivors and volunteers are cleaning up the city.\"}, {\"start\": 521.14, \"end\": 527.4, \"text\": \"Lebanese hospitals are under huge stress dealing with the death of 137 people and treating\"}, {\"start\": 527.41, \"end\": 530.12, \"text\": \"5,000 wounded.\"}, {\"start\": 530.12, \"end\": 536.14, \"text\": \"Those who survived are trying to pick up the pieces.\"}, {\"start\": 536.14, \"end\": 544.02, \"text\": \"Glass and debris crunch below the feet of an army of volunteers who are stepping in\"}, {\"start\": 544.02, \"end\": 553.28, \"text\": \"where the government is not, attempting to clear the rubble of billions of dollars of damage.\"}, {\"start\": 553.28, \"end\": 561.88, \"text\": \"They urge each other on but for others, it's all just too much.\"}, {\"start\": 561.88, \"end\": 567.9, \"text\": \"The intensity of the emotional roller coaster has left them hollow shells.\"}, {\"start\": 567.9, \"end\": 578.14, \"text\": \"But as a cleanup continues, rage continues to grow across the country with people demanding\"}, {\"start\": 578.14, \"end\": 581.08, \"text\": \"accountability and government reform.\"}, {\"start\": 581.08, \"end\": 589.58, \"text\": \"Three days after the deadly blast, there is still no clear explanation or apology.\"}, {\"start\": 589.58, \"end\": 597.0, \"text\": \"French President Emmanuel Macron toured the wreckage.\"}, {\"start\": 597.0, \"end\": 602.14, \"text\": \"He is the first foreign leader to set foot there.\"}, {\"start\": 602.14, \"end\": 612.9, \"text\": \"He was surrounded by hundreds of Lebanese citizens calling for revolution, urging him,\"}, {\"start\": 612.9, \"end\": 616.68, \"text\": \"begging him to do something.\"}, {\"start\": 616.68, \"end\": 625.28, \"text\": \"From outside and inside the country, demands for answers grow louder as calls emerge for\"}, {\"start\": 625.28, \"end\": 629.12, \"text\": \"an independent probe into the explosion.\"}, {\"start\": 629.12, \"end\": 635.9, \"text\": \"International experts say this is not just about accountability or how the country is\"}, {\"start\": 635.9, \"end\": 641.2, \"text\": \"going to rebuild emotionally and physically.\"}, {\"start\": 641.2, \"end\": 652.6, \"text\": \"It's about how Lebanon is going to find its soul.\"}, {\"start\": 655.12, \"end\": 665.88, \"text\": \"Instagram's copycat version of TikTok is now available in the US and in more than 50 other countries.\"}, {\"start\": 665.88, \"end\": 675.0, \"text\": \"The short form video feature is called \\\"Reels\\\" and it was launched on Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 675.0, \"end\": 686.72, \"text\": \"Instagram owner Facebook has a habit of copying features from rivals and Reels is clearly\"}, {\"start\": 686.72, \"end\": 691.36, \"text\": \"a carbon copy of TikTok.\"}, {\"start\": 691.36, \"end\": 704.16, \"text\": \"Just like TikTok, Reels lets Instagram users make 15 second videos set to music or audio\"}, {\"start\": 704.16, \"end\": 710.88, \"text\": \"including special-effects.\"}, {\"start\": 710.88, \"end\": 718.76, \"text\": \"Reels' debut comes as President Trump just make good on his threat to issue an executive\"}, {\"start\": 718.76, \"end\": 723.22, \"text\": \"order banning TikTok.\"}, {\"start\": 723.22, \"end\": 730.74, \"text\": \"The order says the video sharing social media app cannot operate in the United States for\"}, {\"start\": 730.74, \"end\": 737.1, \"text\": \"45 days unless it is sold by its Chinese parent company.\"}, {\"start\": 737.1, \"end\": 747.96, \"text\": \"Microsoft has a reportedly been in talks to purchase TikTok from Byte Dance.\"}, {\"start\": 754.38, \"end\": 767.46, \"text\": \"The 1987 hit movie \\\"Dirty Dancing\\\" is getting a sequel.\"}, {\"start\": 767.46, \"end\": 774.26, \"text\": \"The CEO of Lionsgate announced plans for the new movie Thursday.\"}, {\"start\": 774.26, \"end\": 785.2, \"text\": \"Last month the studio shared Jennifer Grey will star and executive produce an untitled\"}, {\"start\": 785.2, \"end\": 787.36, \"text\": \"dance movie.\"}, {\"start\": 787.36, \"end\": 797.62, \"text\": \"During Thursday's conference call the CEO said that it was indeed a \\\"Dirty Dancing\\\" movie.\"}, {\"start\": 797.62, \"end\": 803.58, \"text\": \"Grey costarred in the original film.\"}, {\"start\": 803.58, \"end\": 823.6, \"text\": \"She played Frances \\\"Baby\\\" Housman who has a summer fling with Patrick Swayze's character Johnny.\"}, {\"start\": 823.6, \"end\": 832.9, \"text\": \"Swayze died of pancreatic cancer in 2009.\"}, {\"start\": 832.9, \"end\": 845.36, \"text\": \"The studio's CEO says the new film will \\\"be exactly the kind of romantic, nostalgic movie\"}, {\"start\": 845.36, \"end\": 852.26, \"text\": \"that Dirty Dancing fans have been waiting for.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 854.72, \"end\": 857.56, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 857.56, \"end\": 859.94, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 859.94, \"end\": 863.58, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 863.58, \"end\": 875.46, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our app too.\"}, {\"start\": 875.46, \"end\": 882.4, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your Language.\"}]"
  },
  "woBf_0sHPOU": {
    "video_id": "woBf_0sHPOU",
    "title": "Overturned truck sparks unbelievable fireball (ASL - 2.12.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180213",
    "duration": 67,
    "view_count": 227,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.02, \"end\": 10.3, \"text\": \"A truck loaded with liquefied natural gas overturned in China and sparked any enormous\"}, {\"start\": 10.3, \"end\": 12.62, \"text\": \"explosion.\"}, {\"start\": 12.62, \"end\": 17.93, \"text\": \"The fireball spread incredibly fast and engulfed, not only the vehicle, but trees lining the\"}, {\"start\": 17.93, \"end\": 19.4, \"text\": \"roadway.\"}, {\"start\": 19.4, \"end\": 22.1, \"text\": \"You have to see the video to believe it.\"}, {\"start\": 22.1, \"end\": 23.4, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 44.44, \"end\": 51.92, \"text\": \"Two people were rushed to the hospital with burns and other injuries.\"}, {\"start\": 51.92, \"end\": 62.52, \"text\": \"Several other cars were burned nearby but the occupants escaped unharmed.\"}, {\"start\": 62.52, \"end\": 64.76, \"text\": \"Wow!\"}]"
  },
  "b7FlASvY17I": {
    "video_id": "b7FlASvY17I",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.10.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180411",
    "duration": 601,
    "view_count": 1355,
    "description": "4.10.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Zuckerberg testifies, takes responsibility for scandal \n-Biggest \"Black Lives Matter\" Facebook page is a fake\n-Trump promises \"force\" in Syria\n-Tax season, beware of scams \n-Kids jump from burning dance studio\n-Tommy Hilfiger expands disability friendly clothing\n-Cutest broken leg ever!\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.64, \"end\": 8.64, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.64, \"end\": 11.08, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.08, \"end\": 12.58, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.58, \"end\": 15.64, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.0, \"end\": 32.34, \"text\": \"Facebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg was on the hot seat in Washington, DC today.\"}, {\"start\": 32.34, \"end\": 39.93, \"text\": \"He faced grilling by US lawmakers on several topics including the Cambridge Analytica data\"}, {\"start\": 39.93, \"end\": 46.14, \"text\": \"scandal, Russia's interference in the 2016 presidential election and general questions\"}, {\"start\": 46.14, \"end\": 52.1, \"text\": \"on how Facebook protects its users from scams and fake news.\"}, {\"start\": 52.1, \"end\": 58.5, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg said he alone is responsible for what happened on Facebook and he admits the\"}, {\"start\": 58.52, \"end\": 62.9, \"text\": \"company didn't do enough to protect its users from harm.\"}, {\"start\": 62.9, \"end\": 69.5, \"text\": \"He said the company's top priority has always been to connect people, build community and\"}, {\"start\": 69.5, \"end\": 76.22, \"text\": \"bring the world closer together and advertisers will never take priority over that as long\"}, {\"start\": 76.34, \"end\": 79.16, \"text\": \"as he is running Facebook.\"}, {\"start\": 79.16, \"end\": 88.94, \"text\": \"He also seemed to support the idea of legislation that would limit the scope and power of Facebook.\"}, {\"start\": 90.84, \"end\": 94.92, \"text\": \"But now a new discovery raises more questions about the integrity of Facebook's platform\"}, {\"start\": 94.92, \"end\": 97.36, \"text\": \"and the content hosted there.\"}, {\"start\": 97.36, \"end\": 104.9, \"text\": \"It turns out the biggest \\\"Black Lives Matter\\\" page on Facebook is fake.\"}, {\"start\": 104.9, \"end\": 115.5, \"text\": \"The fake \\\"Black Lives Matter\\\" page had almost 700,000 followers on Facebook, more than twice\"}, {\"start\": 115.5, \"end\": 118.48, \"text\": \"as many as the official \\\"Black Lives Matter\\\" page.\"}, {\"start\": 118.48, \"end\": 129.7, \"text\": \"CNN has learned it was a scam with ties to a middle-aged white man in Australia.\"}, {\"start\": 129.7, \"end\": 140.2, \"text\": \"A review of the page and associated accounts and websites shows it was tied to online fundraisers.\"}, {\"start\": 140.2, \"end\": 143.48, \"text\": \"The page brought in at least $100,000 that supposedly went to \\\"Black Lives Matter\\\" causes\"}, {\"start\": 143.48, \"end\": 144.94, \"text\": \"in the US.\"}, {\"start\": 144.94, \"end\": 155.32, \"text\": \"But CNN has learned at least some of the money was transferred to Australian bank accounts.\"}, {\"start\": 155.32, \"end\": 158.5, \"text\": \"Facebook has since suspended the page.\"}, {\"start\": 158.5, \"end\": 162.66, \"text\": \"The \\\"Black Lives Matter\\\" official page includes a blue check mark showing it has been verified\"}, {\"start\": 162.66, \"end\": 166.28, \"text\": \"as authentic by Facebook.\"}, {\"start\": 168.26, \"end\": 177.08, \"text\": \"President Trump met with his senior military leaders on Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 177.08, \"end\": 182.0, \"text\": \"He said they are now making a decision as to what they will do with respect to the horrible\"}, {\"start\": 182.0, \"end\": 185.64, \"text\": \"chemical attack in Syria over the weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 185.64, \"end\": 192.72, \"text\": \"Trump said whatever actions they take, it will be forceful.\"}, {\"start\": 192.72, \"end\": 198.1, \"text\": \"Other major world leaders are considering action as well.\"}, {\"start\": 198.16, \"end\": 209.38, \"text\": \"Trump spoke to British Prime Minister Theresa May and both leaders agree the use of chemical\"}, {\"start\": 209.38, \"end\": 214.4, \"text\": \"weapons must not continue.\"}, {\"start\": 214.4, \"end\": 223.94, \"text\": \"And over the weekend the United Nations Security Council continued to debate on how to respond\"}, {\"start\": 223.94, \"end\": 227.8, \"text\": \"to what happened in Syria.\"}, {\"start\": 227.8, \"end\": 234.18, \"text\": \"But the Syrian government continues to deny any involvement.\"}, {\"start\": 234.18, \"end\": 243.98, \"text\": \"And regarding possible US military strikes, a senior Syrian minister says \\\"We are not afraid.\"}, {\"start\": 243.98, \"end\": 246.52, \"text\": \"We will never be afraid.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 249.04, \"end\": 256.58, \"text\": \"Not only is it tax season, it's tax scam season.\"}, {\"start\": 256.64, \"end\": 264.48, \"text\": \"According to the IRS, thousands of people have been scammed out of millions of dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 264.48, \"end\": 268.74, \"text\": \"So here are some helpful tips so you don't become a victim of a tax scam.\"}, {\"start\": 268.74, \"end\": 275.74, \"text\": \"If a refund shows up in your bank account that you know you did not deserve, beware.\"}, {\"start\": 275.74, \"end\": 285.46, \"text\": \"Chances are thieves filed a fraudulent tax return using your information.\"}, {\"start\": 285.46, \"end\": 289.7, \"text\": \"When the refund goes into your bank account someone will call you claiming to be with\"}, {\"start\": 289.7, \"end\": 293.88, \"text\": \"the IRS to retrieve the money.\"}, {\"start\": 293.88, \"end\": 301.14, \"text\": \"If you give the money to the scammers and the government spots the fraud, you are still\"}, {\"start\": 301.14, \"end\": 306.52, \"text\": \"on the hook for returning the money to the IRS.\"}, {\"start\": 306.52, \"end\": 317.64, \"text\": \"And know this: the IRS will never demand immediate payment, threatened to call police or immigration\"}, {\"start\": 317.64, \"end\": 325.38, \"text\": \"or ask for unusual payments like gift cards or wire transfers.\"}, {\"start\": 325.38, \"end\": 332.78, \"text\": \"They will not initially contact you through email, text, social media or the phone.\"}, {\"start\": 332.78, \"end\": 337.72, \"text\": \"Typically the IRS will send a notice in the mail.\"}, {\"start\": 337.74, \"end\": 344.02, \"text\": \"If someone claiming to be from the IRS calls you, hang up immediately, look up the IRS\"}, {\"start\": 344.02, \"end\": 348.44, \"text\": \"phone number and call them directly.\"}, {\"start\": 348.78, \"end\": 359.2, \"text\": \"To learn more about tax scams go to IRS.gov and type in \\\"scam\\\" in the search field.\"}, {\"start\": 360.84, \"end\": 366.9, \"text\": \"A fire broke out in a New Jersey dance studio Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 366.9, \"end\": 378.26, \"text\": \"Cell phone video captured children screaming for help and jumping from the balcony to escape\"}, {\"start\": 378.26, \"end\": 381.06, \"text\": \"the flames.\"}, {\"start\": 420.52, \"end\": 426.0, \"text\": \"Firefighters broke a window to the second floor to rescue the last two girl stuck in\"}, {\"start\": 426.06, \"end\": 428.56, \"text\": \"the building.\"}, {\"start\": 428.62, \"end\": 437.5, \"text\": \"Five people were taken to the hospital with minor injuries but everyone survived.\"}, {\"start\": 437.5, \"end\": 441.32, \"text\": \"The cause of the fire still under investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 443.46, \"end\": 457.32, \"text\": \"Tommy Hilfiger released its new \\\"Adaptive Collection\\\" clothing line last week.\"}, {\"start\": 457.32, \"end\": 464.4, \"text\": \"The clothes make dressing easy for everyone, including those with disabilities.\"}, {\"start\": 464.4, \"end\": 471.34, \"text\": \"It includes dresses, jackets and jeans that feature magnetic closures and magnetic buttons.\"}, {\"start\": 471.34, \"end\": 479.94, \"text\": \"The pants have velcro closures and magnetic flies and zippers, along with adjustable leg\"}, {\"start\": 479.94, \"end\": 484.82, \"text\": \"openings and hems.\"}, {\"start\": 484.82, \"end\": 508.44, \"text\": \"Paralympian Jeremy Campbell, paraplegic dancer Chelsie Hill and others were hired to model the line.\"}, {\"start\": 508.5, \"end\": 518.7, \"text\": \"Tommy Hilfiger says the collection empowers differently abled adults to express themselves\"}, {\"start\": 518.7, \"end\": 520.28, \"text\": \"through fashion.\"}, {\"start\": 522.06, \"end\": 524.06, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 524.06, \"end\": 528.22, \"text\": \"This may be the cutest broken leg ever!\"}, {\"start\": 528.22, \"end\": 534.26, \"text\": \"This little squirrel in Western New York is on the mend after suffering a broken leg.\"}, {\"start\": 534.26, \"end\": 543.42, \"text\": \"It happened after a windstorm swept through the area, damaging trees and knocking out power.\"}, {\"start\": 543.58, \"end\": 548.22, \"text\": \"A resident her crying sounds after a tree fell.\"}, {\"start\": 548.22, \"end\": 553.3, \"text\": \"What she found was two baby squirrels in a nest.\"}, {\"start\": 553.34, \"end\": 557.64, \"text\": \"She brought the injured animals to local vet for treatment.\"}, {\"start\": 557.64, \"end\": 561.52, \"text\": \"That's where this teeny tiny squirrel got her teeny tiny leg cast.\"}, {\"start\": 561.52, \"end\": 570.48, \"text\": \"Doctors named the squirrel \\\"Katarina\\\" and say she should be fine in a couple of weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 573.48, \"end\": 575.44, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 575.44, \"end\": 577.34, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 577.34, \"end\": 579.72, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 579.72, \"end\": 584.04, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 584.08, \"end\": 586.2, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 586.24, \"end\": 587.92, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 588.12, \"end\": 592.16, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "gHITisrphJw": {
    "video_id": "gHITisrphJw",
    "title": "GVRA proposed policy change infuriates deaf community (ASL - 3.7.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180308",
    "duration": 71,
    "view_count": 77,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.12, \"end\": 7.08, \"text\": \"If you live in Georgia, we have some important information to share with you regarding the\"}, {\"start\": 7.08, \"end\": 11.3, \"text\": \"Georgia Vocational Rehabilitation Agency (GVRA).\"}, {\"start\": 11.3, \"end\": 23.26, \"text\": \"The agency is proposing a change to remove Gallaudet University and National Technical\"}, {\"start\": 23.26, \"end\": 26.6, \"text\": \"Institute for the Deaf from its list of approved schools for college funding.\"}, {\"start\": 26.6, \"end\": 34.42, \"text\": \"Instead the agency wants to expand in-state college options and use interpreters.\"}, {\"start\": 34.42, \"end\": 39.74, \"text\": \"The proposed change will impact the Deaf community and it is urging people to let their voices\"}, {\"start\": 39.74, \"end\": 43.5, \"text\": \"be heard and fight by showing up in mass at the upcoming public hearings.\"}, {\"start\": 43.5, \"end\": 48.36, \"text\": \"Here are the dates, times and locations:\"}, {\"start\": 48.36, \"end\": 60.8, \"text\": \"March 13th, March 15th, March 20th, March 21st, March 22nd and April 19th.\"}, {\"start\": 60.8, \"end\": 67.82, \"text\": \"If you cannot make the public hearings, you can complete a comment form on the GVRA website.\"}, {\"start\": 67.82, \"end\": 70.48, \"text\": \"Here is the address.\"}]"
  },
  "IjUZClqdbpk": {
    "video_id": "IjUZClqdbpk",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.13.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180314",
    "duration": 449,
    "view_count": 1457,
    "description": "3.13.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Trump fires Secretary of State Tillerson\n-Tillerson aide fired\n-Trump aide fired\n-Third Nor'easter this month hits New England\n-Rapper Craig Mack dead at 46\n-Man tries to stop hit and run with sledge hammer\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.3, \"end\": 9.3, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.3, \"end\": 11.36, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.38, \"end\": 13.44, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 13.44, \"end\": 15.82, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.14, \"end\": 23.4, \"text\": \"Washington DC was full of shakeups today.\"}, {\"start\": 23.4, \"end\": 25.5, \"text\": \"We'll start with the biggest.\"}, {\"start\": 25.5, \"end\": 35.96, \"text\": \"President Trump fired Secretary of State Rex Tiller just hours after Tillerson returned\"}, {\"start\": 36.02, \"end\": 38.64, \"text\": \"from a trip to Africa.\"}, {\"start\": 38.64, \"end\": 45.78, \"text\": \"Trump and Tillerson have been at odds for months over a number of issues, particularly\"}, {\"start\": 45.78, \"end\": 52.28, \"text\": \"the handling of North Korea and its leader Kim Jong-Un.\"}, {\"start\": 52.28, \"end\": 62.62, \"text\": \"Tillerson and Defense Chief Jim Mattis were pushing for a more measured, less aggressive\"}, {\"start\": 62.62, \"end\": 65.08, \"text\": \"approach than the president.\"}, {\"start\": 65.08, \"end\": 69.48, \"text\": \"And Trump said last week's announcement for plans to meet with Kim Jong-Un and was made\"}, {\"start\": 69.5, \"end\": 73.84, \"text\": \"without counseling his top diplomat.\"}, {\"start\": 73.84, \"end\": 81.28, \"text\": \"Sources also say Trump had been talking about replacing Tillerson with CIA Director Mike\"}, {\"start\": 81.28, \"end\": 87.59, \"text\": \"Pompeo for months.\"}, {\"start\": 87.59, \"end\": 92.409, \"text\": \"However Pompeo still has to be approved by the Senate before taking over as Secretary\"}, {\"start\": 92.409, \"end\": 94.36, \"text\": \"of State.\"}, {\"start\": 94.36, \"end\": 100.22, \"text\": \"Tillerson says his last day will be March 31.\"}, {\"start\": 102.88, \"end\": 108.52, \"text\": \"Hours after Tillerson was let go, the White House also got rid of Tillerson's aide Steve\"}, {\"start\": 108.66, \"end\": 112.68, \"text\": \"Goldstein.\"}, {\"start\": 112.68, \"end\": 120.58, \"text\": \"He was fired after he publicly contradicted the White House's account of Tillerson's firing.\"}, {\"start\": 120.58, \"end\": 124.02, \"text\": \"Goldstein sent out a tweet that said Tillerson never spoke to the president and found out\"}, {\"start\": 124.02, \"end\": 126.96, \"text\": \"he was fired on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 127.28, \"end\": 132.72, \"text\": \"Asked Tuesday how Tillerson learned of his dismissal, Trump didn't directly answer the\"}, {\"start\": 132.72, \"end\": 135.04, \"text\": \"question.\"}, {\"start\": 136.96, \"end\": 150.68, \"text\": \"A few hours later President Trump's longtime personal aide John McEntee was fired.\"}, {\"start\": 150.68, \"end\": 156.04, \"text\": \"A source says McEntee was fired because he's being investigated by the Department of Homeland\"}, {\"start\": 156.04, \"end\": 158.92, \"text\": \"Security.\"}, {\"start\": 158.92, \"end\": 163.24, \"text\": \"The source says the probe involves serious financial crimes that are not related to the\"}, {\"start\": 163.24, \"end\": 165.24, \"text\": \"president.\"}, {\"start\": 165.24, \"end\": 170.84, \"text\": \"However two other sources say McEntee was pushed out because of issues with his security\"}, {\"start\": 170.84, \"end\": 174.08, \"text\": \"clearance.\"}, {\"start\": 174.08, \"end\": 187.349, \"text\": \"McEntee is the latest in a string of administrators and aides to leave the administration.\"}, {\"start\": 187.36, \"end\": 193.36, \"text\": \"As of today, a total of 39 White House staffers have left the Trump\"}, {\"start\": 193.36, \"end\": 197.8, \"text\": \"administration since he took office.\"}, {\"start\": 197.8, \"end\": 208.32, \"text\": \"Over the last 14 days, five top officials have either been fired or resigned.\"}, {\"start\": 209.68, \"end\": 214.0, \"text\": \"We're one week away from the first day of spring\"}, {\"start\": 214.0, \"end\": 220.32, \"text\": \"and the northeast just can't catch a break.\"}, {\"start\": 220.56, \"end\": 231.76, \"text\": \"A third coastal storm in less than two weeks will bring more snow, more flooding and howling\"}, {\"start\": 231.76, \"end\": 236.4, \"text\": \"winds to New England, impacting millions.\"}, {\"start\": 236.4, \"end\": 240.08, \"text\": \"Officials are warning people, again, about dangerous driving conditions.\"}, {\"start\": 240.08, \"end\": 248.16, \"text\": \"State governent offices are closed and businesses are being asked to allow their employees to\"}, {\"start\": 248.16, \"end\": 250.64, \"text\": \"stay home.\"}, {\"start\": 250.64, \"end\": 259.92, \"text\": \"Massachusetts' governor is telling non-emergency state employees not to report to work.\"}, {\"start\": 259.92, \"end\": 267.44, \"text\": \"The storm has canceled hundreds of flights and knocked out power for thousands.\"}, {\"start\": 270.64, \"end\": 275.12, \"text\": \"Legendary rapper Craig Mack died today.\"}, {\"start\": 275.12, \"end\": 278.16, \"text\": \"He was 46 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 278.16, \"end\": 286.0, \"text\": \"Sources say he had been ill for some time and died of heart failure.\"}, {\"start\": 286.0, \"end\": 296.72, \"text\": \"Mack was one of the artists who helped launch Sean Combs' \\\"Bad Boy\\\" record label.\"}, {\"start\": 296.72, \"end\": 308.64, \"text\": \"His 1990's hit song \\\"Flava In Ya Ear\\\" is considered one of the greatest singles in hip-hop history.\"}, {\"start\": 308.64, \"end\": 314.32, \"text\": \"But by the year 2000, Mack had left hip-hop industry.\"}, {\"start\": 314.32, \"end\": 325.68, \"text\": \"He decided to devote his life to God and because of that he no longer felt comfortable rapping.\"}, {\"start\": 327.12, \"end\": 334.74, \"text\": \"It was a wild scene on the streets of Miami this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 334.78, \"end\": 337.12, \"text\": \"Two cars got into an accident.\"}, {\"start\": 337.12, \"end\": 340.8, \"text\": \"One car tried to leave the scene.\"}, {\"start\": 340.8, \"end\": 345.4, \"text\": \"That's when two men started yelling at the driver to stop, pounding on his car trying\"}, {\"start\": 345.4, \"end\": 348.5, \"text\": \"to open the car doors.\"}, {\"start\": 348.5, \"end\": 353.2, \"text\": \"The driver manages to pull away onto another street.\"}, {\"start\": 353.2, \"end\": 357.4, \"text\": \"A crowd follows.\"}, {\"start\": 357.4, \"end\": 366.18, \"text\": \"That's when one person pulls out a sledgehammer and begins breaking the windows of the car.\"}, {\"start\": 366.24, \"end\": 367.18, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 398.2, \"end\": 405.0, \"text\": \"The driver eventually pulls away again but was later arrested.\"}, {\"start\": 405.0, \"end\": 410.52, \"text\": \"He faces charges of fleeing and eluding police, leaving the scene of an accident and reckless\"}, {\"start\": 410.62, \"end\": 412.9, \"text\": \"driving.\"}, {\"start\": 412.9, \"end\": 418.78, \"text\": \"The arrest report says he may have been high on drugs.\"}, {\"start\": 421.48, \"end\": 423.74, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 423.84, \"end\": 425.04, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 425.04, \"end\": 427.82, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 427.82, \"end\": 433.82, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 433.82, \"end\": 440.34, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "qmyNG6BxU4k": {
    "video_id": "qmyNG6BxU4k",
    "title": "“S***hole” projected onto Trump Hotel (ASL - 1.15.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180115",
    "duration": 120,
    "view_count": 252,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.84, \"end\": 10.66, \"text\": \"We want to warn you that some of the language in the story is vulgar and unsuitable for\"}, {\"start\": 10.66, \"end\": 13.3, \"text\": \"children.\"}, {\"start\": 13.3, \"end\": 21.2, \"text\": \"So please use discretion when viewing it.\"}, {\"start\": 21.2, \"end\": 37.6, \"text\": \"On Saturday night, the Trump International Hotel in Washington DC had the word \\\"shithole\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 37.6, \"end\": 42.74, \"text\": \"projected on the front of the building along with several grinning poop emojis.\"}, {\"start\": 42.74, \"end\": 44.72, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 55.44, \"end\": 65.12, \"text\": \"Also projected on the building were things like \\\"Pay Trump bribes here\\\" and \\\"We are all\"}, {\"start\": 65.44, \"end\": 75.76, \"text\": \"responsible to stand up to end white supremacy.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 75.76, \"end\": 90.74, \"text\": \"A man from Washington named Robin Bell is taking credit for the stunt.\"}, {\"start\": 90.74, \"end\": 101.0, \"text\": \"He told CNN the projection was up for less than an hour and it was all in response to\"}, {\"start\": 101.0, \"end\": 112.6, \"text\": \"Trump's reported racist comments during discussions on immigration reform.\"}, {\"start\": 112.6, \"end\": 118.96, \"text\": \"Trump has denied making the comment.\"}]"
  },
  "FiT5DnAmGAY": {
    "video_id": "FiT5DnAmGAY",
    "title": "Trump goes on twitter tirade (ASL - 2.22.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180223",
    "duration": 193,
    "view_count": 175,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.02, \"end\": 11.46, \"text\": \"President Trump spent the past 24 hours tweeting furiously in response to comments and criticisms\"}, {\"start\": 11.46, \"end\": 23.18, \"text\": \"involving the Parkland, Florida shooting, gun sale background checks and the NRA.\"}, {\"start\": 23.18, \"end\": 31.6, \"text\": \"The first tweet is in response to comments he made during his listening session yesterday\"}, {\"start\": 31.6, \"end\": 40.74, \"text\": \"with survivors of gun violence in which he suggested arming teachers with guns.\"}, {\"start\": 40.74, \"end\": 51.48, \"text\": \"He tweeted: \\\"I never said 'give teacher's guns' like was stated on fake news @CNN and @NBC.\"}, {\"start\": 51.48, \"end\": 59.54, \"text\": \"What I said was to look at the possibility of giving 'concealed guns to gun teachers\"}, {\"start\": 59.54, \"end\": 65.48, \"text\": \"with military or special training experience, only the best.\"}, {\"start\": 65.48, \"end\": 74.74, \"text\": \"20% of teachers, a lot, would now be able to immediately fire back if a savage sicko\"}, {\"start\": 74.749, \"end\": 80.039, \"text\": \"came to a school with bad intentions.\"}, {\"start\": 80.04, \"end\": 88.08, \"text\": \"Highly trained teachers would also serve as a deterrent to the cowards that do this.\"}, {\"start\": 88.08, \"end\": 95.08, \"text\": \"Far more assets at much less cost than guards.\"}, {\"start\": 95.08, \"end\": 101.48, \"text\": \"A 'gun free' school is a magnet for bad people.\"}, {\"start\": 101.48, \"end\": 106.08, \"text\": \"Attacks would end!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 106.08, \"end\": 116.2, \"text\": \"He later addressed background checks by tweeting\\\" \\\"I will be strongly pushing Comprehensive\"}, {\"start\": 116.2, \"end\": 120.6, \"text\": \"Background Checks with an emphasis on mental health.\"}, {\"start\": 120.6, \"end\": 134.68, \"text\": \"Raise age to 21 and end sale of Bump Stocks!\"}, {\"start\": 134.68, \"end\": 143.44, \"text\": \"Congress is in a mood to finally do something on this issue, I hope!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 143.44, \"end\": 152.62, \"text\": \"Many people have been critical of the National Rifle Association's (NRA) resistance to certain\"}, {\"start\": 152.62, \"end\": 158.14, \"text\": \"gun limitations, specifically the AR-15.\"}, {\"start\": 158.14, \"end\": 167.02, \"text\": \"This was Trump's response\\\" 'What many people don't understand, or don't want to understand,\"}, {\"start\": 167.02, \"end\": 178.04, \"text\": \"is that Wayne, Chris and the folks who work so hard at the NRA are great people and great\"}, {\"start\": 178.04, \"end\": 180.6, \"text\": \"American patriots.\"}, {\"start\": 180.6, \"end\": 184.72, \"text\": \"They love our country and will do the right thing.\"}, {\"start\": 184.78, \"end\": 188.6, \"text\": \"Make America great again!\\\"\"}]"
  },
  "jAJPCu0bJT8": {
    "video_id": "jAJPCu0bJT8",
    "title": "Sign1News 8.4.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180805",
    "duration": 576,
    "view_count": 798,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Survivors of Parkland shooting rally at NRA headquarters\n-Bush doctor shooting suspect dead\n-Judge rules DACA must be restored \n-Trump attacks LeBron James and Don Lemon over interview\n-Date rape drug may stop suicides\n-Rescued Thai boys end novice monk period\n-Happy Birthday Barack Obama!",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.2, \"end\": 8.66, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.66, \"end\": 11.1, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.16, \"end\": 12.84, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.84, \"end\": 15.46, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.5, \"end\": 30.54, \"text\": \"Thousands of protesters converged on the National Rifle Association's (NRA) headquarters in\"}, {\"start\": 30.54, \"end\": 33.44, \"text\": \"Fairfax, Virginia today.\"}, {\"start\": 33.46, \"end\": 40.52, \"text\": \"The rally is called the \\\"National Rally on the NRA.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 40.52, \"end\": 50.94, \"text\": \"Many of the protesters included members of \\\"March For Our Lives\\\" and survivors of the\"}, {\"start\": 50.94, \"end\": 59.18, \"text\": \"Marjory Stoneman Douglas high school shooting in Parkland, Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 59.18, \"end\": 68.4, \"text\": \"They were there to advocate for stricter gun control laws, to push for the revocation of\"}, {\"start\": 68.4, \"end\": 75.68, \"text\": \"NRA's tax-exempt status and to remember victims of gun violence.\"}, {\"start\": 75.68, \"end\": 82.22, \"text\": \"Since it is Saturday, most NRA workers were not in the office.\"}, {\"start\": 83.84, \"end\": 95.5, \"text\": \"The urgent manhunt for a suspect accused of executing President George HW Bush's former\"}, {\"start\": 95.5, \"end\": 107.0, \"text\": \"doctor Mark Hausknecht is over.\"}, {\"start\": 107.0, \"end\": 112.62, \"text\": \"Joseph Pappas was found dead Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 112.62, \"end\": 120.24, \"text\": \"Police say a tip from a Houston parks employee led them to the suspect after the employee\"}, {\"start\": 120.26, \"end\": 126.18, \"text\": \"mistook Pappas for a vandal.\"}, {\"start\": 126.26, \"end\": 133.64, \"text\": \"The witness then found the suspect's wallet with ID after he fled and notified police\"}, {\"start\": 133.64, \"end\": 144.36, \"text\": \"after recognizing Pappas's name and photograph from media coverage.\"}, {\"start\": 144.36, \"end\": 151.44, \"text\": \"When two police officers approached Pappas in a southwest Houston neighborhood, he killed himself.\"}, {\"start\": 151.5, \"end\": 155.96, \"text\": \"The suspect had 30 years of law enforcement experience as a Texas constable and was a\"}, {\"start\": 155.96, \"end\": 158.56, \"text\": \"trained marksman.\"}, {\"start\": 158.56, \"end\": 168.26, \"text\": \"Police say investigators also discovered an intelligence file he was keeping on Dr. Hausknecht.\"}, {\"start\": 168.34, \"end\": 176.94, \"text\": \"The doctor's execution took place in broad daylight last month as he was riding his bike to work.\"}, {\"start\": 176.94, \"end\": 183.58, \"text\": \"Dashcam captured the moments before the shooting and Pappas can be seen apparently stalking\"}, {\"start\": 183.68, \"end\": 185.56, \"text\": \"the doctor on his bike too.\"}, {\"start\": 185.56, \"end\": 192.08, \"text\": \"Investigators say Pappas planned the execution possibly as revenge for his mother's death\"}, {\"start\": 192.08, \"end\": 196.7, \"text\": \"20 years ago under Dr. Hausknecht's care.\"}, {\"start\": 198.66, \"end\": 206.379, \"text\": \"A federal judge says the Deferred Action for Children Arrivals program (DACA) should be\"}, {\"start\": 206.38, \"end\": 207.86, \"text\": \"fully restored.\"}, {\"start\": 207.86, \"end\": 215.12, \"text\": \"That's the ruling from District Judge John Bates in Washington DC.\"}, {\"start\": 215.12, \"end\": 224.36, \"text\": \"He says the Trump administration has yet to justify its proposal to end DACA.\"}, {\"start\": 224.38, \"end\": 232.44, \"text\": \"He's giving the White House 20 days to appeal.\"}, {\"start\": 232.44, \"end\": 237.88, \"text\": \"DACA is an Obama-era program.\"}, {\"start\": 237.88, \"end\": 246.9, \"text\": \"It protects about 800,000 undocumented immigrants who were brought to the US as children from\"}, {\"start\": 246.9, \"end\": 249.08, \"text\": \"deportation.\"}, {\"start\": 249.78, \"end\": 258.62, \"text\": \"Earlier this week NBA superstar Lebron James sat down for a candid interview with CNN's\"}, {\"start\": 258.62, \"end\": 261.28, \"text\": \"Don Lemon.\"}, {\"start\": 261.28, \"end\": 268.72, \"text\": \"James talked about everything from sports to politics.\"}, {\"start\": 268.72, \"end\": 274.07, \"text\": \"In one part of the interview Lemon asked James what would he say to the president if he was\"}, {\"start\": 274.07, \"end\": 276.6, \"text\": \"sitting across from him.\"}, {\"start\": 276.6, \"end\": 287.04, \"text\": \"James said he would never sit across from Trump but he would sit across from Barack Obama.\"}, {\"start\": 287.04, \"end\": 295.9, \"text\": \"Friday night Trump took aim at James and Lemon on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 295.9, \"end\": 303.46, \"text\": \"He tweeted: \\\"Lebron James was just interviewed by the dumbest man on television, Don Lemon.\"}, {\"start\": 303.46, \"end\": 308.07, \"text\": \"He made Lebron look smart, which isn't easy to do.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 308.07, \"end\": 316.31, \"text\": \"He ended his tweet with \\\"I like Mike!,\\\" possibly a reference to the ongoing debate over who\"}, {\"start\": 316.31, \"end\": 324.62, \"text\": \"is the greatest NBA player of all time, James or Michael Jordan.\"}, {\"start\": 324.62, \"end\": 332.52, \"text\": \"First Lady Melania Trump does not appear to be letting the president's statement about\"}, {\"start\": 332.52, \"end\": 336.96, \"text\": \"James affect her own feelings on the matter.\"}, {\"start\": 336.96, \"end\": 345.96, \"text\": \"She praised James for his charity work and says it looks like he's working to do good\"}, {\"start\": 345.96, \"end\": 349.28, \"text\": \"things on behalf of our next generation.\"}, {\"start\": 350.74, \"end\": 360.68, \"text\": \"Doctors are using a common date rape drug to stop suicides.\"}, {\"start\": 360.69, \"end\": 371.77, \"text\": \"Ketamine is widely thought of as a club drug, a date rape drug, but at a couple hundred\"}, {\"start\": 371.77, \"end\": 381.64, \"text\": \"centers around the country, doctors have been using it to help patients at real risk of\"}, {\"start\": 381.66, \"end\": 385.6, \"text\": \"dying by suicide.\"}, {\"start\": 385.6, \"end\": 388.82, \"text\": \"It's been referred to as a \\\"save shot.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 388.82, \"end\": 396.49, \"text\": \"Ketamine seems to target areas of the brain that have withered away due to depression,\"}, {\"start\": 396.49, \"end\": 401.03, \"text\": \"and grow new synapses.\"}, {\"start\": 401.03, \"end\": 409.78, \"text\": \"One patient said his infusion worked quickly and his depression symptoms went from severe\"}, {\"start\": 409.78, \"end\": 414.12, \"text\": \"to mild to nonexistent over a few months.\"}, {\"start\": 414.12, \"end\": 416.3, \"text\": \"But none of this comes cheap.\"}, {\"start\": 416.3, \"end\": 423.3, \"text\": \"It cost nearly $500 per infusion with most patients needing up to six infusions to start\"}, {\"start\": 423.3, \"end\": 428.46, \"text\": \"and boosters every few weeks after.\"}, {\"start\": 428.46, \"end\": 431.9, \"text\": \"For now, insurance doesn't cover any of it.\"}, {\"start\": 434.42, \"end\": 449.16, \"text\": \"Eleven of the rescued Thai boys just ended their novice monk period today.\"}, {\"start\": 449.16, \"end\": 458.4, \"text\": \"They took part in a ceremony in Chiang Rai after which they left the temple to return\"}, {\"start\": 458.4, \"end\": 461.42, \"text\": \"to their families.\"}, {\"start\": 461.42, \"end\": 464.56, \"text\": \"Twelve boys and their football coach were rescued from the cave last month.\"}, {\"start\": 464.56, \"end\": 474.94, \"text\": \"The monk period was meant to honor Lieutenant Commander Saman Kunan who died during the\"}, {\"start\": 474.94, \"end\": 476.94, \"text\": \"cave rescue operation.\"}, {\"start\": 476.94, \"end\": 485.04, \"text\": \"But not all the boys were ordained as Buddhist monks because the 12th team member is Christian.\"}, {\"start\": 486.92, \"end\": 494.3, \"text\": \"Today is former President Barack Obama's birthday.\"}, {\"start\": 494.3, \"end\": 496.14, \"text\": \"He's 57 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 496.14, \"end\": 503.78, \"text\": \"The 44th president of the United States was born in Hawaii on August 4, 1961.\"}, {\"start\": 503.78, \"end\": 511.2, \"text\": \"Obama has been staying busy since leaving office in January 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 511.2, \"end\": 522.36, \"text\": \"Just a few weeks ago, he spoke before a crowd of around 15,000 people in Johannesburg, South\"}, {\"start\": 522.36, \"end\": 529.66, \"text\": \"Africa to honor the life of Nelson Mandela.\"}, {\"start\": 529.66, \"end\": 540.28, \"text\": \"He and his wife Michelle Obama also enjoyed some time in France and took in a concert\"}, {\"start\": 540.28, \"end\": 545.3, \"text\": \"by Beyonce and Jay-Z in Paris.\"}, {\"start\": 547.58, \"end\": 550.02, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 550.02, \"end\": 551.86, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 551.86, \"end\": 554.52, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 554.52, \"end\": 559.82, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 559.82, \"end\": 562.64, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 562.64, \"end\": 564.04, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 564.08, \"end\": 567.54, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "bBqc-znpE-I": {
    "video_id": "bBqc-znpE-I",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.5.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171106",
    "duration": 421,
    "view_count": 138,
    "description": "November 5, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-TEXAS CHURCH SHOOTING\n-TRUMP AND ABE GOLF\n-MELANIA TRUMP PROTECTED BY ALL-FEMALE SQUAD\n-TRUMP'S APPROVAL HITS HISTORIC LOW\n-WEEKEND BOX OFFICE\n-NATIONAL DOUGHNUT DAY  \n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN, FOX, ABC, CBS, TBN (TRINITY BROADCA",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 15.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.0, \"end\": 22.0, \"text\": \"This morning at First Baptist Church in\"}, {\"start\": 22.0, \"end\": 29.0, \"text\": \"Sutherland Springs, Texas\"}, {\"start\": 29.0, \"end\": 34.0, \"text\": \"a man walked in during the 11:30 service and started shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 34.0, \"end\": 39.0, \"text\": \"Twenty eight people died. Dozens more were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 39.0, \"end\": 44.0, \"text\": \"The pastor's 14 year old daughter was one of the 28 killed.\"}, {\"start\": 44.0, \"end\": 49.0, \"text\": \"Police say family members were taken to a community center\"}, {\"start\": 49.0, \"end\": 54.0, \"text\": \"to await word on the condition of their family members. When the man\"}, {\"start\": 54.0, \"end\": 59.0, \"text\": \"finished shooting police say he jumped in a car and sped off.  A police\"}, {\"start\": 59.0, \"end\": 64.0, \"text\": \"chase ensued through a neighborhood. The man died. But at this point\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 69.0, \"text\": \"police aren't saying if police killed him or if he killed himself.\"}, {\"start\": 72.0, \"end\": 75.0, \"text\": \"President Trump kicked off his two week tour of\"}, {\"start\": 76.0, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"Asia on the golf course.\"}, {\"start\": 81.0, \"end\": 86.0, \"text\": \"His goal is to solidify his relationship with the\"}, {\"start\": 86.0, \"end\": 91.0, \"text\": \"Japanese prime minister Shinzo Abe.\"}, {\"start\": 92.0, \"end\": 96.0, \"text\": \"The two signed matching baseball hats, shared a meal\"}, {\"start\": 97.0, \"end\": 102.0, \"text\": \"and played a round of golf. They were joined by\"}, {\"start\": 102.0, \"end\": 108.0, \"text\": \"professional golfer Hideki Matsuyama.\"}, {\"start\": 109.0, \"end\": 114.0, \"text\": \"Trump also met with American and Japanese servicemembers at a\"}, {\"start\": 114.0, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"joint U.S. Japanese military base outside Tokyo.\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 124.0, \"text\": \"During his two week trip Trump will\"}, {\"start\": 125.0, \"end\": 130.0, \"text\": \"carry out high stakes talks with leaders of Japan, South Korea\"}, {\"start\": 130.0, \"end\": 135.0, \"text\": \"and China and attend summits in Vietnam\"}, {\"start\": 135.0, \"end\": 139.0, \"text\": \"and the Philippines. Trump says he also expects to meet with\"}, {\"start\": 139.0, \"end\": 145.0, \"text\": \"Russian President Vladimir Putin during the trip.\"}, {\"start\": 145.0, \"end\": 150.0, \"text\": \"He told reporters he wants Putin's help on\"}, {\"start\": 150.0, \"end\": 154.0, \"text\": \"North Korea.\"}, {\"start\": 154.0, \"end\": 158.0, \"text\": \"That meeting is expected to take place Thursday during the Asia\"}, {\"start\": 158.0, \"end\": 163.0, \"text\": \"Pacific Economic Cooperation summit in Vietnam.\"}, {\"start\": 166.0, \"end\": 170.0, \"text\": \"Melania Trump arrived in Japan today for a\"}, {\"start\": 170.0, \"end\": 175.0, \"text\": \"two day visit with President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 175.0, \"end\": 180.0, \"text\": \"The police department in Tokyo has put together\"}, {\"start\": 180.0, \"end\": 186.0, \"text\": \"an all female squad of officers to protect the first lady during her visit.\"}, {\"start\": 186.0, \"end\": 190.0, \"text\": \"On Wednesday the female police unit practiced their moves\"}, {\"start\": 190.0, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"in front of Tokyo's Imperial Palace for the media.\"}, {\"start\": 197.0, \"end\": 204.0, \"text\": \"They brushed up on defensive maneuvers and drills.\"}, {\"start\": 204.0, \"end\": 207.0, \"text\": \"However a law enforcement analyst says\"}, {\"start\": 208.0, \"end\": 212.0, \"text\": \"the U.S. Secret Service will still be the first line of\"}, {\"start\": 212.0, \"end\": 219.0, \"text\": \"defense for the first lady while she's in Japan.\"}, {\"start\": 223.0, \"end\": 226.0, \"text\": \"Here in the United States President Trump's approval\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 231.0, \"text\": \"ratings are dropping to historic lows.\"}, {\"start\": 231.0, \"end\": 237.0, \"text\": \"According to a new Washington Post-ABC News poll\"}, {\"start\": 237.0, \"end\": 241.0, \"text\": \"fifty nine percent of Americans\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 246.0, \"text\": \"disapprove of his job performance\"}, {\"start\": 246.0, \"end\": 251.0, \"text\": \"while 37 percent approve. Those are the\"}, {\"start\": 251.0, \"end\": 256.0, \"text\": \"lowest approval ratings for any president\"}, {\"start\": 259.0, \"end\": 264.0, \"text\": \"after nine months in office. About two thirds of\"}, {\"start\": 264.0, \"end\": 269.0, \"text\": \"respondents said he is not honest, he is not trustworthy and does\"}, {\"start\": 269.0, \"end\": 274.0, \"text\": \"not have the temperament to be the president.\"}, {\"start\": 275.0, \"end\": 278.0, \"text\": \"When asked about\"}, {\"start\": 278.0, \"end\": 283.0, \"text\": \"Special Counsel Robert Mueller's\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 288.0, \"text\": \"investigation regarding Russian involvement in\"}, {\"start\": 289.0, \"end\": 293.0, \"text\": \"the 2016 presidential election\"}, {\"start\": 294.0, \"end\": 298.0, \"text\": \"49 percent of respondents believe Trump committed a crime while\"}, {\"start\": 298.0, \"end\": 302.0, \"text\": \"44 percent say that's unlikely.\"}, {\"start\": 303.0, \"end\": 308.0, \"text\": \"However only 19 percent of respondents think\"}, {\"start\": 308.0, \"end\": 313.0, \"text\": \"that there is solid evidence of a crime.\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 320.0, \"text\": \"It was a big weekend for movies at the box office.\"}, {\"start\": 320.0, \"end\": 326.0, \"text\": \"Thor Ragnsrock opened at the top spot\"}, {\"start\": 326.0, \"end\": 331.0, \"text\": \"raking in a projected $121 million.\"}, {\"start\": 332.0, \"end\": 336.0, \"text\": \"The R-rated comedy\"}, {\"start\": 337.0, \"end\": 345.0, \"text\": \"A Bad Moms Christmas is a distant second, pulling in about $17 million.\"}, {\"start\": 346.0, \"end\": 351.0, \"text\": \"The horror flick Jigsaw is number three, making an\"}, {\"start\": 351.0, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"estimated 6.7 million dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 357.0, \"end\": 362.0, \"text\": \"Today is National Doughnut Day.\"}, {\"start\": 362.024, \"end\": 369.024, \"text\": \"The first one was back in June. So why two days?\"}, {\"start\": 370.0, \"end\": 375.0, \"text\": \"It's not clear. The June date was established by the Salvation Army\"}, {\"start\": 376.0, \"end\": 381.0, \"text\": \"and honors women volunteers who served doughnuts to soldiers\"}, {\"start\": 381.0, \"end\": 386.0, \"text\": \"during World War 2. No word on who started today's day. But do we really care?\"}, {\"start\": 386.0, \"end\": 391.0, \"text\": \"So go ahead. If you love doughnuts, it's time to celebrate your favorite one.\"}, {\"start\": 395.0, \"end\": 399.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 399.0, \"end\": 403.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Remember to like us on Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 403.0, \"end\": 406.0, \"text\": \"and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 406.024, \"end\": 412.024, \"text\": \"Sign1 News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "1yZiY7j0AoM": {
    "video_id": "1yZiY7j0AoM",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.15.18 - News in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180115",
    "duration": 558,
    "view_count": 2353,
    "description": "1.15.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Photos of Calif. mudslide residents still missing\n-\"S***hole\" projected onto Trump Hotel\n-Mitt Romney tells friend he will run for senate\n-MLK Day National Day of Service\n-Passengers jump from burning casino boat\n-Brawl over cherries erupts in Australian grocery story\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and informati",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.76, \"end\": 6.52, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.52, \"end\": 8.34, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.34, \"end\": 9.56, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 9.56, \"end\": 12.12, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 13.7, \"end\": 27.28, \"text\": \"Twenty people have died as a result of the mudslides that devastated Montecito, California.\"}, {\"start\": 27.32, \"end\": 33.92, \"text\": \"Fire officials say four people are still missing and they want to show their pictures in hopes\"}, {\"start\": 33.92, \"end\": 36.9, \"text\": \"of someone recognizing them.\"}, {\"start\": 36.9, \"end\": 39.28, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 39.28, \"end\": 49.64, \"text\": \"Rescue workers are actively searching for (from left to right):\"}, {\"start\": 49.64, \"end\": 65.04, \"text\": \"17-year-old John \\\"Jack\\\" Cantin, 53-year-old John \\\"Jack\\\" Keating, 28-year-old Faviola Benitez\"}, {\"start\": 65.04, \"end\": 72.98, \"text\": \"Calderon and 2-year-old Lydia Sutthithepa.\"}, {\"start\": 72.98, \"end\": 80.76, \"text\": \"Lydia's father and brother were killed in the mudslides.\"}, {\"start\": 83.9, \"end\": 93.68, \"text\": \"We want to warn you that some of the language in the story is vulgar and unsuitable for\"}, {\"start\": 93.68, \"end\": 96.56, \"text\": \"children.\"}, {\"start\": 96.56, \"end\": 104.52, \"text\": \"So please use discretion when viewing it.\"}, {\"start\": 104.54, \"end\": 121.02, \"text\": \"On Saturday night, the Trump International Hotel in Washington DC had the word \\\"shithole\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 121.02, \"end\": 125.58, \"text\": \"projected on the front of the building along with several grinning poop emojis.\"}, {\"start\": 125.6, \"end\": 128.08, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 138.64, \"end\": 148.32, \"text\": \"Also projected on the building were things like \\\"Pay Trump bribes here\\\" and \\\"We are all\"}, {\"start\": 148.32, \"end\": 159.2, \"text\": \"responsible to stand up to end white supremacy.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 159.2, \"end\": 173.6, \"text\": \"A man from Washington named Robin Bell is taking credit for the stunt.\"}, {\"start\": 173.68, \"end\": 184.4, \"text\": \"He told CNN the projection was up for less than an hour and it was all in response to\"}, {\"start\": 184.4, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"Trump's reported racist comments during discussions on immigration reform.\"}, {\"start\": 196.0, \"end\": 202.56, \"text\": \"Trump has denied making the comment.\"}, {\"start\": 204.86, \"end\": 212.8, \"text\": \"Mitt Romney has reportedly told a friend that he's getting back into politics.\"}, {\"start\": 212.8, \"end\": 224.66, \"text\": \"According to the New York Times, Romney texted that friend the words \\\"I'm running.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 224.66, \"end\": 236.0, \"text\": \"There has been growing speculation he will seek the vacant U.S. Senate seat in Utah.\"}, {\"start\": 236.0, \"end\": 244.56, \"text\": \"The position is open because Republican Senator Orrin Hatch recently announced he would not\"}, {\"start\": 244.56, \"end\": 247.16, \"text\": \"seek reelection.\"}, {\"start\": 247.16, \"end\": 253.1, \"text\": \"The deadline to enter the race is in March.\"}, {\"start\": 253.1, \"end\": 261.92, \"text\": \"No word on when Romney will make an official statement.\"}, {\"start\": 264.48, \"end\": 276.8, \"text\": \"Today the nation honors the late Dr. Martin Luther King, Junior.\"}, {\"start\": 276.8, \"end\": 282.4, \"text\": \"He was killed in April 1968.\"}, {\"start\": 282.56, \"end\": 293.44, \"text\": \"The civil rights icon would've been 89 years old if alive today.\"}, {\"start\": 293.44, \"end\": 306.72, \"text\": \"This year marks the 50th anniversary of his assassination.\"}, {\"start\": 306.72, \"end\": 315.2, \"text\": \"MLK Day is celebrated on the third Monday in January.\"}, {\"start\": 315.2, \"end\": 321.6, \"text\": \"This year, it falls on his actual birthday, the 15th.\"}, {\"start\": 321.6, \"end\": 331.04, \"text\": \"President Ronald Reagan signed the holiday into law in 1983.\"}, {\"start\": 331.04, \"end\": 342.94, \"text\": \"The first national MLK holiday was observed three years later in 1986.\"}, {\"start\": 342.94, \"end\": 349.42, \"text\": \"Government offices and the US stock market are closed today.\"}, {\"start\": 349.42, \"end\": 357.8, \"text\": \"President Trump is encouraging Americans to observe the federal holiday by doing \\\"acts\"}, {\"start\": 357.8, \"end\": 361.54, \"text\": \"of civic work and community service.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 363.62, \"end\": 377.62, \"text\": \"A casino shuttle boat caught fire on Sunday off the coast of New Port Richey, Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 377.62, \"end\": 383.5, \"text\": \"We have a dramatic video of people jumping into the water to escape the flames.\"}, {\"start\": 383.52, \"end\": 384.88, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 397.68, \"end\": 402.82, \"text\": \"The cause of the fire is still unclear.\"}, {\"start\": 402.82, \"end\": 415.9, \"text\": \"The boat's captain said he had trouble with the engine, saw smoke and headed closer to\"}, {\"start\": 416.0, \"end\": 417.8, \"text\": \"shore.\"}, {\"start\": 417.8, \"end\": 428.68, \"text\": \"Authorities say all 50 passengers and crew members jumped off the boat but one woman\"}, {\"start\": 428.68, \"end\": 434.94, \"text\": \"died at the hospital from her injuries.\"}, {\"start\": 437.56, \"end\": 449.62, \"text\": \"A dispute over cherries turned into a brawl at a grocery store in Australia.\"}, {\"start\": 449.62, \"end\": 458.58, \"text\": \"Two men approached an employee wanting to buy the fruit by the bag.\"}, {\"start\": 458.58, \"end\": 470.08, \"text\": \"But the employee said they had to buy them by the kilo and if they weren't happy with\"}, {\"start\": 470.08, \"end\": 472.76, \"text\": \"that they could leave.\"}, {\"start\": 472.76, \"end\": 475.72, \"text\": \"They were not happy.\"}, {\"start\": 475.72, \"end\": 483.68, \"text\": \"After a brief conversation, one of the men ended up punching the store employee in the\"}, {\"start\": 483.88, \"end\": 491.68, \"text\": \"face and that's when the brawl started.\"}, {\"start\": 491.68, \"end\": 492.96, \"text\": \"Take look.\"}, {\"start\": 513.52, \"end\": 524.48, \"text\": \"Fellow customers struggled to break up the fight.\"}, {\"start\": 524.64, \"end\": 530.24, \"text\": \"The worker ended up with a head wound and had to be taken to the hospital.\"}, {\"start\": 530.24, \"end\": 532.96, \"text\": \"The two shoppers were arrested.\"}, {\"start\": 535.04, \"end\": 537.52, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 537.52, \"end\": 538.8, \"text\": \"I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 538.8, \"end\": 541.2, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 541.2, \"end\": 545.68, \"text\": \"Remember to like us of Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 545.68, \"end\": 551.44, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "K9IL3PsNd6k": {
    "video_id": "K9IL3PsNd6k",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.28.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171129",
    "duration": 475,
    "view_count": 793,
    "description": "November 28, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-NORTH KOREA LAUNCHES BALLISTIC MISSILE\n-TAX REFORM BILL VOTE NEARS\n-WEINSTEIN RESIGNS DIRECTORS GUILD OF AMERICA\n-SEARCH FOR ESCAPED INMATE WITH SKELETON FACE TATTOO\n-UK FIRST TO ALLOW VIAGRA WITHOUT PRESCRIPTION\n-SCRAMBLE FOR MARKLE'S COAT CAUSES SITE TO CRASH\n-BATHROBE BURGLAR GOES THROUGH HOME WINDOW\n-POLICE STOP CAR WITH MASSIVE CHRISTMAS TREE ON TOP\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.32, \"end\": 7.08, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.12, \"end\": 9.66, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.68, \"end\": 11.0, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 11.0, \"end\": 15.0, \"text\": \"And here you top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.68, \"end\": 21.72, \"text\": \"North Korea fired a ballistic missile early Wednesday local time.\"}, {\"start\": 21.8, \"end\": 31.36, \"text\": \"That's according to South Korea's Joint Chiefs of Staff, which said a missile was launched\"}, {\"start\": 31.4, \"end\": 39.84, \"text\": \"from Pyongsong, South Pyongan -- and headed east.\"}, {\"start\": 39.88, \"end\": 46.52, \"text\": \"US military confirms a possible missile launch from North Korea.\"}, {\"start\": 46.6, \"end\": 53.24, \"text\": \"US defense and intelligence officials have been growing increasingly puzzled as to why\"}, {\"start\": 53.24, \"end\": 62.56, \"text\": \"North Korean leader Kim Jong-Un had not tested a ballistic missile in nearly 2 months.\"}, {\"start\": 62.64, \"end\": 68.2, \"text\": \"Before Wednesday's test, North Korea had fired 22 missiles without active warheads during\"}, {\"start\": 68.36, \"end\": 75.56, \"text\": \"15 test since February.\"}, {\"start\": 75.72, \"end\": 82.68, \"text\": \"US officials say North Korea is continuing to develop missiles, rocket fuel and engines,\"}, {\"start\": 82.72, \"end\": 86.4, \"text\": \"as well as targeting and guidance systems.\"}, {\"start\": 86.52, \"end\": 94.92, \"text\": \"The US believes Pyongyang may be able to put a miniaturized warhead on a missile sometime\"}, {\"start\": 94.96, \"end\": 97.96, \"text\": \"in 2018 -- giving it a theoretical capability to launch a missile with a warhead top that\"}, {\"start\": 97.96, \"end\": 100.4, \"text\": \"could attack the US.\"}, {\"start\": 100.4, \"end\": 108.84, \"text\": \"White House Press Secretary Sarah Sanders tweeted on Tuesday saying that\"}, {\"start\": 108.92, \"end\": 113.68, \"text\": \"President Trump was briefed while the missile was still in the air.\"}, {\"start\": 115.56, \"end\": 124.24, \"text\": \"This is a crucial week on Capitol Hill for the fate of the new tax bill.\"}, {\"start\": 124.28, \"end\": 131.28, \"text\": \"Republicans and the White House are trying to find the votes to score the first legislative\"}, {\"start\": 131.28, \"end\": 133.72, \"text\": \"win of the Trump presidency.\"}, {\"start\": 134.0, \"end\": 142.68, \"text\": \"But there are not enough \\\"Yes\\\" votes yet and several Republican senators are still undecided.\"}, {\"start\": 142.76, \"end\": 149.68, \"text\": \"Plus the Congressional budget office released a new analysis predicting the bill would increase\"}, {\"start\": 149.68, \"end\": 155.72, \"text\": \"the deficit by $1.4 trillion over 10 years.\"}, {\"start\": 155.92, \"end\": 162.44, \"text\": \"And removing Obamacare's individual mandate would decrease the number of people without\"}, {\"start\": 162.44, \"end\": 175.48, \"text\": \"health insurance by 4 million in 2019 and 13 million over the next decade.\"}, {\"start\": 176.96, \"end\": 189.0, \"text\": \"Movie producer Harvey Weinstein has resigned from the Directors Guild of America.\"}, {\"start\": 189.16, \"end\": 195.4, \"text\": \"A Guild spokesperson confirmed his resignation went into effect on Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 195.44, \"end\": 200.52, \"text\": \"Weinstein has already been removed from a number of other professional organizations\"}, {\"start\": 200.56, \"end\": 206.04, \"text\": \"as sex scandals and lawsuits grow.\"}, {\"start\": 206.16, \"end\": 211.88, \"text\": \"Over 50 women have accuse Weinstein of sexual misconduct.\"}, {\"start\": 212.0, \"end\": 217.928, \"text\": \"A spokesperson for Weinstein says any allegations of nonconsensual sex\"}, {\"start\": 217.928, \"end\": 221.84, \"text\": \"are unequivocally denied by Mr. Weinstein.\"}, {\"start\": 221.96, \"end\": 233.28, \"text\": \"Weinstein is under investigation by the NYPD, the LAPD, the Beverly Hills police and UK\"}, {\"start\": 233.28, \"end\": 235.92, \"text\": \"police for acts of sexual assaults in their respective jurisdictions.\"}, {\"start\": 237.48, \"end\": 249.04, \"text\": \"Authorities in San Joaquin County, California are looking for this man.\"}, {\"start\": 249.12, \"end\": 252.6, \"text\": \"His name is Corey Hughes.\"}, {\"start\": 252.6, \"end\": 256.36, \"text\": \"He's an escaped inmate with skeleton-like face tattoos.\"}, {\"start\": 256.36, \"end\": 260.4, \"text\": \"Hughes is serving time on a weapons charge.\"}, {\"start\": 260.56, \"end\": 267.0, \"text\": \"The Sheriff's office says he went missing from his prison workgroup Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 267.12, \"end\": 270.96, \"text\": \"He was last seen in the city of Stockton.\"}, {\"start\": 270.96, \"end\": 274.32, \"text\": \"He was scheduled to be released from custody in February.\"}, {\"start\": 274.4, \"end\": 284.28, \"text\": \"Anyone who sees Hughes is asked to call the San Joaquin County Sheriff's office.\"}, {\"start\": 286.16, \"end\": 294.16, \"text\": \"The UK will be the first country to sell Viagra over the counter.\"}, {\"start\": 294.2, \"end\": 301.6, \"text\": \"Pfizer, who makes the erectile dysfunction drug,\"}, {\"start\": 301.64, \"end\": 304.52, \"text\": \"said Tuesday that buyers will not need a prescription.\"}, {\"start\": 304.56, \"end\": 310.4, \"text\": \"UK health officials say making Viagra more freely available will stop users from trying\"}, {\"start\": 310.4, \"end\": 315.32, \"text\": \"to get it through unregulated, illegal channels, like those found on the Internet.\"}, {\"start\": 315.32, \"end\": 319.88, \"text\": \"Sales are set to begin next spring.\"}, {\"start\": 321.92, \"end\": 330.32, \"text\": \"Megan Markle is already setting fashion trends.\"}, {\"start\": 330.4, \"end\": 337.03, \"text\": \"The white belted coat she wore Monday, after announcing her engagement to Prince Harry,\"}, {\"start\": 337.04, \"end\": 341.2, \"text\": \"is a hot commodity.\"}, {\"start\": 341.32, \"end\": 346.4, \"text\": \"It is from the Canadian label \\\"Line.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 346.4, \"end\": 350.8, \"text\": \"The coat costs more the $600 and is now sold out.\"}, {\"start\": 350.84, \"end\": 356.48, \"text\": \"Admirers crashed the company's website searching for it.\"}, {\"start\": 356.56, \"end\": 364.12, \"text\": \"Markle and Prince Harry are set to get married next May.\"}, {\"start\": 366.12, \"end\": 376.96, \"text\": \"Police in Ramapo, New York are investigating a bizarre break-in.\"}, {\"start\": 377.08, \"end\": 383.4, \"text\": \"A camera was rolling when a man with a mohawk, beard and gray robe\"}, {\"start\": 383.4, \"end\": 389.48, \"text\": \"shimmied through the kitchen window of a home.\"}, {\"start\": 389.64, \"end\": 395.96, \"text\": \"He was looking directly into the camera before making his way into the home.\"}, {\"start\": 396.04, \"end\": 400.24, \"text\": \"Police did not say what, if anything, he took from the home.\"}, {\"start\": 400.4, \"end\": 404.12, \"text\": \"But the police department is currently investigating it as a residential burglary.\"}, {\"start\": 406.12, \"end\": 414.24, \"text\": \"Police in Massachusetts posted this picture Friday on Facebook of a vehicle that they\"}, {\"start\": 414.32, \"end\": 420.6, \"text\": \"spotted about 25 miles west of Boston.\"}, {\"start\": 420.64, \"end\": 427.52, \"text\": \"They pulled it over because it had a gigantic Christmas tree on top.\"}, {\"start\": 427.8, \"end\": 429.4, \"text\": \"The tree clearly covers the entire car and even hangs off the sides.\"}, {\"start\": 429.48, \"end\": 433.72, \"text\": \"It's not clear whether it dangles on the driver's windshield.\"}, {\"start\": 433.92, \"end\": 442.76, \"text\": \"Police on Facebook reminded people to transport holiday trees responsibly.\"}, {\"start\": 442.76, \"end\": 446.64, \"text\": \"It's unclear if the driver was given a ticket.\"}, {\"start\": 449.16, \"end\": 451.52, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 451.56, \"end\": 452.96, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 453.04, \"end\": 455.88, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 455.88, \"end\": 461.36, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 461.48, \"end\": 468.56, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "py5xnRUlYkQ": {
    "video_id": "py5xnRUlYkQ",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.1.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171202",
    "duration": 378,
    "view_count": 261,
    "description": "December 1, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n -MICHEAL FLYNN CHARGED\n-THE GOP SAYS THEY HAVE THE VOTES FOR TAX REFORM \n-GERALDO APOLOGIZES TO BETTE MIDLER AFTER GROPING ALLEGATION\n-AMERICAN AIRLINES BAN SMART LUGGAGE\n-WORLD AIDS DAY\n-TODAY IS NATIONAL PIE DAY!\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVE",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.06, \"end\": 8.44, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.46, \"end\": 9.56, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 9.56, \"end\": 12.9, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 12.92, \"end\": 19.76, \"text\": \"Today former Trump National Security Advisor Michael Flynn\"}, {\"start\": 19.76, \"end\": 25.4, \"text\": \"plead guilty to making false statements to the FBI.\"}, {\"start\": 25.4, \"end\": 32.16, \"text\": \"The court file says that Flynn lied about two meetings he had with the Russian Ambassador\"}, {\"start\": 32.16, \"end\": 36.82, \"text\": \"Sergey Kislyak in December 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 36.86, \"end\": 44.88, \"text\": \"The prosecutor said Flynn had many discussions with Kislyak about US sanctions against Russia.\"}, {\"start\": 44.92, \"end\": 49.66, \"text\": \"In one of the meetings he discussed sanctions the US imposed against Russia.\"}, {\"start\": 49.66, \"end\": 54.42, \"text\": \"Flynn said in court that he accepts full responsibility for his actions.\"}, {\"start\": 54.48, \"end\": 61.74, \"text\": \"Trump's lawyer, Ty Cobb, said nothing about the guilty plea or the charge implicates anyone\"}, {\"start\": 61.74, \"end\": 66.04, \"text\": \"other than Mr. Flynn.\"}, {\"start\": 67.84, \"end\": 75.26, \"text\": \"Today the Republican Senate efforts to secure support for tax reform appears successful.\"}, {\"start\": 75.32, \"end\": 80.14, \"text\": \"Fifty-one GOP members said they'll support passing the bill.\"}, {\"start\": 80.14, \"end\": 87.14, \"text\": \"Fifty-one is enough to pass the tax reform bill.\"}, {\"start\": 87.16, \"end\": 91.74, \"text\": \"Earlier this week the Senate Budget Committee passed measure by partyline vote,\"}, {\"start\": 91.8, \"end\": 96.48, \"text\": \"with all 12 Republicans on the panel voting in favor, 11 Democrats voting no.\"}, {\"start\": 96.5, \"end\": 102.6, \"text\": \"Republican leaders hope to hold a vote on potential final passage later today.\"}, {\"start\": 103.7, \"end\": 113.36, \"text\": \"Fox News correspondent Geraldo Rivera apologized Friday to Bette Midler\"}, {\"start\": 113.4, \"end\": 120.38, \"text\": \"after she re-accused him earlier this week of drugging and groping her in the 1970s.\"}, {\"start\": 120.4, \"end\": 131.68, \"text\": \"Rivera's recent tweets about the firing of \\\"Today\\\" anchor Matt Lauer prompted Twitter users\"}, {\"start\": 131.68, \"end\": 146.32, \"text\": \"to post an old interview of Midler talking to talk show host Barbara Walters about the incident.\"}, {\"start\": 146.34, \"end\": 156.52, \"text\": \"In the clip, Midler said Rivera and his producer pushed her into her bathroom and put two inhalant\"}, {\"start\": 156.54, \"end\": 159.62, \"text\": \"drugs, \\\"Poppers\\\" under her nose, then groped her.\"}, {\"start\": 159.66, \"end\": 168.62, \"text\": \"Rivera responded on twitter saying: \\\"Although I recall the time Bette Midler has alluded\"}, {\"start\": 168.76, \"end\": 170.38, \"text\": \"to much differently than she, that does not\"}, {\"start\": 170.38, \"end\": 172.36, \"text\": \"change the fact that she has a right to speak out\"}, {\"start\": 172.4, \"end\": 177.92, \"text\": \"and demand an apology for me, for in the very least, publicly embarrassing her all those years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 177.92, \"end\": 180.26, \"text\": \"Bette, I apologize.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 180.28, \"end\": 183.72, \"text\": \"Midler has not yet publicly responded to Rivera's apology.\"}, {\"start\": 185.88, \"end\": 190.1, \"text\": \"If you've got luggage with charging devices built in\"}, {\"start\": 190.18, \"end\": 195.96, \"text\": \"you won't be able to carry it with you on American Airlines flight unless the battery\"}, {\"start\": 196.02, \"end\": 198.1, \"text\": \"can be removed.\"}, {\"start\": 198.1, \"end\": 205.94, \"text\": \"Starting next year, passengers won't be able to check smart bags unless the lithium-ion\"}, {\"start\": 206.0, \"end\": 208.82, \"text\": \"battery is taken out.\"}, {\"start\": 208.92, \"end\": 212.0, \"text\": \"The luggage can be brought on board with the battery in but\"}, {\"start\": 212.04, \"end\": 215.16, \"text\": \"passengers have to be able to remove it.\"}, {\"start\": 215.32, \"end\": 220.84, \"text\": \"American Airlines is the first airline to place limits on \\\"smart luggage\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 220.84, \"end\": 227.04, \"text\": \"after concerns about the dangers of lithium-ion batteries.\"}, {\"start\": 227.04, \"end\": 230.72, \"text\": \"Authorities say those batteries can pose a fire risk on airplanes.\"}, {\"start\": 230.72, \"end\": 235.2, \"text\": \"The new rule goes into effect on January 15.\"}, {\"start\": 237.6, \"end\": 245.92, \"text\": \"December 1 is World AIDS Day and what better time than now to know your status.\"}, {\"start\": 245.92, \"end\": 252.48, \"text\": \"The theme for this year's World AIDS Day is \\\"increasing impact through transparency, accountability\"}, {\"start\": 252.48, \"end\": 254.72, \"text\": \"and partnerships.\"}, {\"start\": 254.72, \"end\": 256.8, \"text\": \"Know your status and get tested.\"}, {\"start\": 256.96, \"end\": 266.4, \"text\": \"According to HIV.gov more than 1 million people in the US are HIV-positive and one out of\"}, {\"start\": 266.4, \"end\": 272.16, \"text\": \"seven don't know their HIV status.\"}, {\"start\": 272.16, \"end\": 280.06, \"text\": \"In 2016, nearly 40,000 people in the US tested positive.\"}, {\"start\": 280.16, \"end\": 284.48, \"text\": \"Many people with the highest risk of contracting the virus aren't getting\"}, {\"start\": 284.48, \"end\": 287.68, \"text\": \"tested.\"}, {\"start\": 287.84, \"end\": 294.72, \"text\": \"With the advances in medicine and research, those who are living with HIV can prevent\"}, {\"start\": 294.72, \"end\": 297.28, \"text\": \"it from progressing to AIDS.\"}, {\"start\": 297.28, \"end\": 303.68, \"text\": \"There is no cure for HIV but experts say it's not a death sentence as long as you know your\"}, {\"start\": 304.0, \"end\": 307.2, \"text\": \"status and get tested.\"}, {\"start\": 307.36, \"end\": 318.24, \"text\": \"You can do that by finding a free and confidential testing location near you at gettested.CDC.gov.\"}, {\"start\": 320.48, \"end\": 324.0, \"text\": \"Today is National Pie Day!\"}, {\"start\": 324.32, \"end\": 334.56, \"text\": \"Pumpkin, cherry or Boston Cream -- whatever your pie of choice, this is the day to indulge.\"}, {\"start\": 334.72, \"end\": 342.4, \"text\": \"You may remember celebrating National Pie Day back in January.\"}, {\"start\": 342.56, \"end\": 348.48, \"text\": \"This second excuse to enjoy pie is in the middle of the holiday pie-making season.\"}, {\"start\": 348.64, \"end\": 351.52, \"text\": \"If sweet dessert pies aren't your thing\"}, {\"start\": 351.84, \"end\": 354.88, \"text\": \"National Pie Day authorities say that pot pies count too.\"}, {\"start\": 356.48, \"end\": 358.56, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 358.88, \"end\": 360.2, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 360.2, \"end\": 361.92, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 362.08, \"end\": 366.24, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 366.24, \"end\": 372.8, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-46vrmBr6BU": {
    "video_id": "-46vrmBr6BU",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.24.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171025",
    "duration": 499,
    "view_count": 166,
    "description": "October 24, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-NIGER AMBUSH UPDATE\n-TRUMP AND CORKER FEUD CONTINUES\n-PROTESTER THROWS RUSSIAN FLAGS AT TRUMP\n-TAMPA MURDERS UPDATE \n-DAD ADMITS DISPOSING OF 3-YEAR OLD DAUGHTER'S BODY\n-MAN FLIPS CAR REACHING FOR CIGARETTE \n-HIPPO PHOTOBOMBS ENGAGEMENT PICTURE\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organiz",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 13.0, \"end\": 15.0, \"text\": \"And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.0, \"end\": 25.0, \"text\": \"We have new information about what really happened\"}, {\"start\": 25.0, \"end\": 30.0, \"text\": \"during the attack in Niger, Africa earlier this month.\"}, {\"start\": 30.0, \"end\": 34.0, \"text\": \"According to military officials the U.S. Army team was\"}, {\"start\": 34.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"gathering information on a terrorist leader\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 45.0, \"text\": \"operating in the area when it was attacked by 50 ISIS\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 50.0, \"text\": \"fighters. The team had not received orders to kill or\"}, {\"start\": 50.0, \"end\": 56.0, \"text\": \"capture the terrorist leader.\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 61.0, \"text\": \"Previously military officials said the soldiers had conducted\"}, {\"start\": 61.0, \"end\": 66.0, \"text\": \"29 similar patrols before.\"}, {\"start\": 66.0, \"end\": 70.0, \"text\": \"But now military officials are saying\"}, {\"start\": 70.0, \"end\": 78.0, \"text\": \"those 29 patrols were conducted by a different task force.\"}, {\"start\": 82.0, \"end\": 86.0, \"text\": \"Today on Capitol Hill\"}, {\"start\": 87.0, \"end\": 92.0, \"text\": \"President Trump's top agenda item for discussion\"}, {\"start\": 92.0, \"end\": 96.0, \"text\": \"was supposed to be tax reform.\"}, {\"start\": 97.0, \"end\": 102.0, \"text\": \"Instead the focus turned to his continuing fight with Republican Senator Bob Corker.\"}, {\"start\": 102.0, \"end\": 107.0, \"text\": \"These two have been going back and forth for weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 107.0, \"end\": 111.0, \"text\": \"In a series of tweets Trump accuses Corker\"}, {\"start\": 112.0, \"end\": 117.0, \"text\": \"of attempting to block the Republican plans\"}, {\"start\": 117.0, \"end\": 119.0, \"text\": \"for tax cuts.\"}, {\"start\": 119.0, \"end\": 126.0, \"text\": \"He called Corker a lightweight.\"}, {\"start\": 127.0, \"end\": 129.0, \"text\": \"Someone asked Corker if he regrets supporting Trump\"}, {\"start\": 131.0, \"end\": 138.0, \"text\": \"during the election. Corker said\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 143.0, \"text\": \"he would never do it again.\"}, {\"start\": 143.0, \"end\": 147.0, \"text\": \"Corker says Trump continues to lower\"}, {\"start\": 148.0, \"end\": 154.0, \"text\": \"the standards of this country. House Speaker\"}, {\"start\": 154.0, \"end\": 158.0, \"text\": \"Paul Ryan told both men to\"}, {\"start\": 158.0, \"end\": 163.0, \"text\": \"cool it and focus on the\"}, {\"start\": 163.0, \"end\": 169.0, \"text\": \"Republican party's top priority which is tax reform.\"}, {\"start\": 172.0, \"end\": 177.0, \"text\": \"While President Trump was walking through the U.S. Capitol today\"}, {\"start\": 177.0, \"end\": 180.0, \"text\": \"a protester threw several Russian\"}, {\"start\": 181.0, \"end\": 186.0, \"text\": \"flags at him. White House officials have\"}, {\"start\": 186.0, \"end\": 192.0, \"text\": \"identified the man as Ryan Clayton.\"}, {\"start\": 192.0, \"end\": 195.0, \"text\": \"He is with the group America\"}, {\"start\": 196.0, \"end\": 201.0, \"text\": \"Take Action.\"}, {\"start\": 202.0, \"end\": 207.0, \"text\": \"As the president was walking by Clayton yelled\"}, {\"start\": 208.0, \"end\": 213.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Trump is treason!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 213.0, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"He also yelled \\\"The president conspired with agents of\"}, {\"start\": 217.0, \"end\": 222.0, \"text\": \"the Russian government to steal an election!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 223.0, \"end\": 228.0, \"text\": \"Currently the Justice Department is investigating whether Russia\"}, {\"start\": 228.0, \"end\": 233.0, \"text\": \"played a role in Trump being elected as president.\"}, {\"start\": 233.0, \"end\": 237.0, \"text\": \"White House security says Clayton\"}, {\"start\": 237.0, \"end\": 242.0, \"text\": \"sneaked in by pretending to be with the media.\"}, {\"start\": 247.024, \"end\": 249.024, \"text\": \"In less than two weeks\"}, {\"start\": 250.0, \"end\": 255.0, \"text\": \"three people have been shot and killed\"}, {\"start\": 255.0, \"end\": 258.0, \"text\": \"within a mile radius of the\"}, {\"start\": 262.024, \"end\": 267.024, \"text\": \"Seminole Heights neighborhood.\"}, {\"start\": 267.1, \"end\": 271.1, \"text\": \"Authorities in Tampa are telling people in\"}, {\"start\": 271.1, \"end\": 275.7, \"text\": \"the neighborhood don't live in fear.\"}, {\"start\": 276.0, \"end\": 280.0, \"text\": \"Investigators think all three killings are linked\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 286.0, \"text\": \"but authorities are not calling it the work of a serial killer yet.\"}, {\"start\": 286.0, \"end\": 291.0, \"text\": \"Police are adding extra patrols to the area\"}, {\"start\": 291.0, \"end\": 294.0, \"text\": \"and even escorting kids to school bus stops.\"}, {\"start\": 296.0, \"end\": 301.0, \"text\": \"Neighbors have formed watch groups\"}, {\"start\": 301.0, \"end\": 306.0, \"text\": \"to patrol the streets. Police are hoping the release\"}, {\"start\": 306.0, \"end\": 311.0, \"text\": \"of surveillance video captured near the\"}, {\"start\": 311.0, \"end\": 318.0, \"text\": \"site will lead to an arrest.\"}, {\"start\": 321.0, \"end\": 326.0, \"text\": \"Yesterday authorities in Texas discovered the body\"}, {\"start\": 326.0, \"end\": 331.0, \"text\": \"of a missing 3 year old girl. Sherin Mathews had been\"}, {\"start\": 331.0, \"end\": 337.0, \"text\": \"missing since October 7th.\"}, {\"start\": 337.0, \"end\": 341.0, \"text\": \"Police say the girl's adoptive father\"}, {\"start\": 342.0, \"end\": 347.0, \"text\": \"Wesley Mathews voluntarily turned himself in yesterday\"}, {\"start\": 347.0, \"end\": 352.0, \"text\": \"and admitted his guilt. He said the little\"}, {\"start\": 352.0, \"end\": 357.0, \"text\": \"refused to drink her milk. He told police he made the girl\"}, {\"start\": 357.0, \"end\": 362.0, \"text\": \"stand outside. When he went to find her she was gone.\"}, {\"start\": 362.0, \"end\": 370.0, \"text\": \"Police charged the father with\"}, {\"start\": 370.0, \"end\": 373.0, \"text\": \"injury to a child. His bond has been set\"}, {\"start\": 373.0, \"end\": 378.0, \"text\": \"at one million dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 382.0, \"end\": 389.0, \"text\": \"Take a look at this. Yesterday in Maine\"}, {\"start\": 389.0, \"end\": 395.0, \"text\": \"a man lost control of his pickup truck while trying to light a cigarette.\"}, {\"start\": 395.0, \"end\": 400.0, \"text\": \"Police say the driver dropped his lighter, became distracted, swerved into the\"}, {\"start\": 400.0, \"end\": 405.0, \"text\": \"wrong lane, overcorrected and\"}, {\"start\": 405.0, \"end\": 410.0, \"text\": \"flipped end over end down a steep embankment.\"}, {\"start\": 410.0, \"end\": 414.0, \"text\": \"He crashed through several trees on the way down. The truck was completely destroyed.\"}, {\"start\": 414.0, \"end\": 419.0, \"text\": \"Amazingly the man walked away without any serious injuries.\"}, {\"start\": 421.924, \"end\": 425.924, \"text\": \"At the Cincinnati zoo\"}, {\"start\": 426.0, \"end\": 429.0, \"text\": \"a picture of Fiona the Hippo\"}, {\"start\": 429.0, \"end\": 435.0, \"text\": \"has gone viral.\"}, {\"start\": 435.0, \"end\": 443.0, \"text\": \"Fiona swam over to watch a\"}, {\"start\": 443.0, \"end\": 450.0, \"text\": \"a man pop the question to his girlfriend.\"}, {\"start\": 450.0, \"end\": 457.0, \"text\": \"The couple says they are huge fans of Fiona so they posted the pictures online.\"}, {\"start\": 457.0, \"end\": 465.0, \"text\": \"They said they were happy Fiona could be a part of their special day.\"}, {\"start\": 469.024, \"end\": 470.999, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 471.0, \"end\": 476.0, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 477.0, \"end\": 482.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 483.0, \"end\": 490.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "QeMd2LWFjRQ": {
    "video_id": "QeMd2LWFjRQ",
    "title": "Dr. G answers your questions: What's the difference between coronavirus and Covid-19",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200324",
    "duration": 85,
    "view_count": 575,
    "description": "Posted 3.24.20",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.66, \"end\": 6.14, \"text\": \"There are a few things I've noticed that has confused everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.14, \"end\": 13.04, \"text\": \"First, yes there is a difference between coronavirus and Covid-19.\"}, {\"start\": 13.04, \"end\": 22.6, \"text\": \"The coronavirus is a small germ you can catch and not know it.\"}, {\"start\": 22.64, \"end\": 26.62, \"text\": \"You don't know if you've touched it and you won't feel it.\"}, {\"start\": 26.62, \"end\": 35.58, \"text\": \"If you become sick, the sickness is called Covid-19 and that's different.\"}, {\"start\": 35.64, \"end\": 40.76, \"text\": \"Many people have coronavirus and don't know it.\"}, {\"start\": 40.76, \"end\": 46.22, \"text\": \"They may feel a little sick or they notice they feel worried.\"}, {\"start\": 46.22, \"end\": 54.56, \"text\": \"If you have Covid-19 that means that you have a fever, cough, you having difficulty breathing.\"}, {\"start\": 54.56, \"end\": 59.18, \"text\": \"Those are the three big symptoms for Covid-19.\"}, {\"start\": 59.18, \"end\": 69.22, \"text\": \"If you're wondering if I have it and need to call the doctor, maybe not.\"}, {\"start\": 69.22, \"end\": 70.94, \"text\": \"Just wait at home.\"}, {\"start\": 70.94, \"end\": 77.48, \"text\": \"Most people with Covid-19 don't need to go to the hospital or the emergency room.\"}, {\"start\": 77.48, \"end\": 80.04, \"text\": \"Just wait safely at home.\"}, {\"start\": 80.04, \"end\": 83.54, \"text\": \"If you have breathing problems, it is not safe to stay at home.\"}, {\"start\": 83.54, \"end\": 84.6, \"text\": \"Go to the doctor.\"}]"
  },
  "xKZMWuGk994": {
    "video_id": "xKZMWuGk994",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.26.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180327",
    "duration": 594,
    "view_count": 1484,
    "description": "3.26.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Trump silent on Stormy Daniels interview\n-First Lady spokesperson tweets on Stormy interview\n-More White House staff changes coming?\n-Rapper Killer Mike apologizes for NRA video\n-Court docs: Father of Pulse gunman was FBI informant\n-China’s space station will crash to Earth soon\n-Sign1News fan comment: disability emojis\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to de",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.42, \"end\": 8.8, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.8, \"end\": 10.8, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.8, \"end\": 12.68, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.68, \"end\": 16.2, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.2, \"end\": 31.52, \"text\": \"Last night former porn star Stormy Daniels broke her silence and told the world about\"}, {\"start\": 31.52, \"end\": 37.86, \"text\": \"her alleged affair with Donald Trump 20 years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 37.86, \"end\": 44.14, \"text\": \"As President Trump returned to Washington DC yesterday from his recent trip to Florida,\"}, {\"start\": 44.16, \"end\": 48.24, \"text\": \"reporters barraged him with questions, specifically regarding Daniels' interview.\"}, {\"start\": 66.0, \"end\": 75.44, \"text\": \"Since Daniels' interview, Trump has been radio silent, not even one tweet.\"}, {\"start\": 75.44, \"end\": 82.8, \"text\": \"However during the press briefing today, White House spokesperson Raj Shah addressed the\"}, {\"start\": 82.8, \"end\": 93.84, \"text\": \"interview by saying: \\\"The president strongly, clearly and has consistently denied the claims\"}, {\"start\": 93.84, \"end\": 97.28, \"text\": \"and the only person who has not been inconsistent is the person making the claims.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 99.2, \"end\": 107.04, \"text\": \"First Lady Melania Trump's communications director did respond via twitter but did not\"}, {\"start\": 107.04, \"end\": 113.44, \"text\": \"directly address the Stormy Daniels' interview.\"}, {\"start\": 113.44, \"end\": 128.48, \"text\": \"It said: \\\"While I know the media is enjoying speculation and salacious gossip, I'd like\"}, {\"start\": 128.64, \"end\": 135.68, \"text\": \"to remind people there is a minor child whose name should be kept out of news stories when\"}, {\"start\": 135.68, \"end\": 138.16, \"text\": \"at all possible.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 140.0, \"end\": 148.48, \"text\": \"President Trump is also trying to brush off rumors of another White House staff shakeup.\"}, {\"start\": 148.48, \"end\": 155.6, \"text\": \"Sources say the president is preparing to oust Veterans Affairs secretary David Shulkin\"}, {\"start\": 155.6, \"end\": 158.48, \"text\": \"as early as this week.\"}, {\"start\": 158.48, \"end\": 165.52, \"text\": \"Shulkin has been at odds with senior management at the VA for months now.\"}, {\"start\": 166.0, \"end\": 177.2, \"text\": \"He has publicly accused Trump political appointees of working to get him fired over policy differences.\"}, {\"start\": 177.2, \"end\": 186.0, \"text\": \"He's been on thin ice with the president since an inspector general report detailed how Shulkin\"}, {\"start\": 186.0, \"end\": 191.36, \"text\": \"and his wife used taxpayer dollars for a European trip.\"}, {\"start\": 194.8, \"end\": 206.48, \"text\": \"On Saturday NRA-TV shared video of an interview with rapper Killer Mike.\"}, {\"start\": 206.48, \"end\": 211.6, \"text\": \"In the interview Killer Mike criticized the \\\"National School Walkout\\\" day in which students\"}, {\"start\": 211.6, \"end\": 225.76, \"text\": \"left class to call for more gun control and honor the victims of the Parkland school massacre.\"}, {\"start\": 225.76, \"end\": 231.92, \"text\": \"He said he warned his own children not to walk out.\"}, {\"start\": 231.92, \"end\": 241.2, \"text\": \"On Sunday Killer Mike apologized for the interview because he said it was used to disparage Saturday's\"}, {\"start\": 241.2, \"end\": 248.96, \"text\": \"\\\"March For Our Lives\\\" rallies.\"}, {\"start\": 249.04, \"end\": 254.08, \"text\": \"He said snippets of the interview were taken from a larger conversation about African-American\"}, {\"start\": 254.08, \"end\": 256.8, \"text\": \"gun ownership.\"}, {\"start\": 256.8, \"end\": 266.24, \"text\": \"He said he was sorry for the way the interview was used and that he supported the \\\"March\"}, {\"start\": 266.64, \"end\": 276.16, \"text\": \"For Life\\\" and the youth-driven gun control movement.\"}, {\"start\": 280.16, \"end\": 297.58, \"text\": \"Noor Salman, the wife of Pulse night club shooter Omar Mateen, is on trial in Florida\"}, {\"start\": 297.6, \"end\": 302.48, \"text\": \"for charges related to the 2016 mass shooting in Orlando.\"}, {\"start\": 302.48, \"end\": 309.44, \"text\": \"She is charged with providing support to a foreign terrorist organization and obstruction\"}, {\"start\": 309.44, \"end\": 312.16, \"text\": \"of justice.\"}, {\"start\": 312.16, \"end\": 317.9, \"text\": \"Prosecutors say she knew the massacre was going to happen.\"}, {\"start\": 317.96, \"end\": 321.54, \"text\": \"She has pleaded not guilty.\"}, {\"start\": 321.54, \"end\": 328.16, \"text\": \"Now attorneys for Salman are calling for a dismissal of charges or a mistrial.\"}, {\"start\": 328.16, \"end\": 340.64, \"text\": \"New details from prosecutors reveal Omar Mateen's father was an FBI informant who is currently\"}, {\"start\": 340.64, \"end\": 343.42, \"text\": \"under criminal investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 343.42, \"end\": 347.84, \"text\": \"According to a motion filed by the defense, prosecutors sent them an email Saturday saying\"}, {\"start\": 347.84, \"end\": 363.54, \"text\": \"Seddique Marteen is being investigated for money transfers from Turkey to Afghanistan.\"}, {\"start\": 363.54, \"end\": 374.0, \"text\": \"Transfer documents were found in his home on the day of the Pulse attack.\"}, {\"start\": 374.0, \"end\": 381.14, \"text\": \"This new revelation could upend the case against Salman.\"}, {\"start\": 381.14, \"end\": 387.68, \"text\": \"Her attorneys say they would have taken a completely different legal strategy if they\"}, {\"start\": 387.68, \"end\": 391.16, \"text\": \"had known about her father-in-law's actions earlier.\"}, {\"start\": 391.16, \"end\": 399.8, \"text\": \"The judge said he would review the defense's motion this evening.\"}, {\"start\": 402.52, \"end\": 412.76, \"text\": \"If you see a fireball crashing to earth on April 1, it might not be an April Fools' Day prank.\"}, {\"start\": 412.76, \"end\": 419.62, \"text\": \"A Chinese space station is expected to crash to earth soon.\"}, {\"start\": 419.62, \"end\": 424.84, \"text\": \"But exactly where it will land is unknown.\"}, {\"start\": 424.92, \"end\": 439.78, \"text\": \"The Tiangong-1 is 34 feet long, which is about the size of a school bus, and weighs 9.4 tons.\"}, {\"start\": 439.78, \"end\": 448.66, \"text\": \"China stopped receiving data from the station back in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 448.68, \"end\": 454.82, \"text\": \"The European space agency says there really is no cause for too much concern as the Earth's\"}, {\"start\": 454.82, \"end\": 461.94, \"text\": \"atmosphere will break apart and burn up much of the space station upon reentry.\"}, {\"start\": 461.94, \"end\": 473.1, \"text\": \"However there is a \\\"worst-case\\\" scenario location area from Northern California to Pennsylvania.\"}, {\"start\": 473.1, \"end\": 479.52, \"text\": \"The space agency predicted the space station will reenter Earth's atmosphere between March\"}, {\"start\": 479.56, \"end\": 482.9, \"text\": \"30 and April 3.\"}, {\"start\": 485.58, \"end\": 494.36, \"text\": \"A few days ago we told you about Apple's push to add emojis that represent people with disabilities.\"}, {\"start\": 494.42, \"end\": 502.94, \"text\": \"The emojis would include an ear with a hearing aid, a person in a wheelchair, a prosthetic\"}, {\"start\": 502.94, \"end\": 510.34, \"text\": \"arm, a service dog and a person with a cane.\"}, {\"start\": 510.34, \"end\": 514.36, \"text\": \"I think it's a wonderful idea because it involves so much diversity.\"}, {\"start\": 514.36, \"end\": 517.06, \"text\": \"I like it and am really looking forward to it.\"}, {\"start\": 517.06, \"end\": 523.78, \"text\": \"We asked you to submit your thoughts on the disability emojis and here's what you had to say.\"}, {\"start\": 523.94, \"end\": 535.28, \"text\": \"Stella Reid said: \\\"Yes, yes I love the emojis!\"}, {\"start\": 535.28, \"end\": 539.02, \"text\": \"And that will inspire all deaf people in the world.\"}, {\"start\": 539.12, \"end\": 541.12, \"text\": \"There needs to be each country with their own emojis so they can use their own in their\"}, {\"start\": 541.12, \"end\": 543.82, \"text\": \"languages all over the world.\"}, {\"start\": 543.9, \"end\": 546.02, \"text\": \"I love the idea the idea!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 546.5, \"end\": 554.72, \"text\": \"Rick Greco just that one concern.\"}, {\"start\": 554.72, \"end\": 560.5, \"text\": \"He hopes the emojis do not include an image of a cochlear implant.\"}, {\"start\": 560.5, \"end\": 565.12, \"text\": \"Stella and Rick thank you so much for your comments.\"}, {\"start\": 568.54, \"end\": 571.24, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 571.24, \"end\": 572.94, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 572.94, \"end\": 574.94, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 574.94, \"end\": 579.4, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 579.58, \"end\": 585.62, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "Lx0tEpJhsyU": {
    "video_id": "Lx0tEpJhsyU",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.14.18 - News in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180115",
    "duration": 587,
    "view_count": 2518,
    "description": "1.14.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Trump tweets DACA “Probably Dead\"\n-More winter storms affect millions\n-California mudslide death toll rises to 20\n-Slain Pakistani girl may have been victim of serial killer\n-Univ. of Hawaii students panic after false missile alert\n-Mark Wahlberg donates $1.5M to #Timesup Legal Fund\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line new",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.06, \"end\": 6.64, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.64, \"end\": 8.48, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.54, \"end\": 9.48, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 9.48, \"end\": 12.44, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.96, \"end\": 27.86, \"text\": \"President Donald Trump was on Twitter early Sunday morning, blaming Democrats for stalled\"}, {\"start\": 27.86, \"end\": 30.04, \"text\": \"talks on a potential immigration deal.\"}, {\"start\": 30.04, \"end\": 44.28, \"text\": \"He tweeted: \\\"DACA is probably dead because the Democrats don't really want it, they just\"}, {\"start\": 44.28, \"end\": 50.56, \"text\": \"want to talk and take desperately needed money away from our military.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 50.56, \"end\": 63.66, \"text\": \"In a second tweet a few minutes later, he wrote: \\\"I, as president, want people coming\"}, {\"start\": 63.66, \"end\": 67.1, \"text\": \"into our country who are going to help us become strong and great again, people coming\"}, {\"start\": 67.1, \"end\": 69.38, \"text\": \"in through a system based on merit.\"}, {\"start\": 69.38, \"end\": 78.42, \"text\": \"No more lotteries!\"}, {\"start\": 78.42, \"end\": 82.16, \"text\": \"America first.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 82.16, \"end\": 90.56, \"text\": \"Trump's tweets came just hours after his administration resumed receiving renewal applications for\"}, {\"start\": 90.56, \"end\": 100.36, \"text\": \"\\\"dreamers\\\" under the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals program (DACA).\"}, {\"start\": 100.36, \"end\": 109.12, \"text\": \"The administration announced the end of DACA in September but a federal court order blocked\"}, {\"start\": 109.12, \"end\": 114.18, \"text\": \"the administration from ending the program.\"}, {\"start\": 116.48, \"end\": 124.04, \"text\": \"More winter storms are bringing snow, ice, sleet and rain across parts of the US\"}, {\"start\": 124.04, \"end\": 128.8, \"text\": \"and that's causing chaos for millions of people from the East Coast to the Midwest.\"}, {\"start\": 128.8, \"end\": 134.44, \"text\": \"Temperatures have dropped dramatically, by 40 or 50 degrees in some places.\"}, {\"start\": 134.44, \"end\": 139.96, \"text\": \"Strong winds are whipping up huge waves in Chicago.\"}, {\"start\": 140.0, \"end\": 143.92, \"text\": \"Temperatures in the Northeast are expected to plummet throughout the day as the cold\"}, {\"start\": 143.92, \"end\": 146.12, \"text\": \"front continues to move east.\"}, {\"start\": 146.12, \"end\": 154.4, \"text\": \"Southern states are also dealing with snow, ice and freezing rain as far south as Louisiana.\"}, {\"start\": 154.4, \"end\": 162.44, \"text\": \"A weather-related accident in Tennessee caused a massive car pileup.\"}, {\"start\": 162.44, \"end\": 166.92, \"text\": \"Millions remain under a flood watch in the Northeast.\"}, {\"start\": 166.92, \"end\": 170.56, \"text\": \"Officials warn ice jams could cause river flooding.\"}, {\"start\": 170.56, \"end\": 175.0, \"text\": \"Frigid temperatures are expected to stick around through the beginning of next week.\"}, {\"start\": 175.0, \"end\": 184.56, \"text\": \"Some areas could see wind chills of 30 to 45 degrees below zero.\"}, {\"start\": 186.76, \"end\": 198.04, \"text\": \"According to California fire officials, 20 people are confirmed dead as a result of the\"}, {\"start\": 198.04, \"end\": 199.32, \"text\": \"devastating mudslides.\"}, {\"start\": 199.32, \"end\": 206.52, \"text\": \"Flash floods triggered the mudslides early Tuesday, damaging or destroying dozens of\"}, {\"start\": 206.52, \"end\": 208.48, \"text\": \"homes.\"}, {\"start\": 208.48, \"end\": 221.84, \"text\": \"Those killed ranged in age from 3 to 89, and all lived in Montecito in Santa Barbara County,\"}, {\"start\": 221.84, \"end\": 224.8, \"text\": \"northwest of Los Angeles.\"}, {\"start\": 225.2, \"end\": 233.52, \"text\": \"Crews continue to search through mud and debris.\"}, {\"start\": 233.56, \"end\": 237.68, \"text\": \"As of Sunday, four people were still missing.\"}, {\"start\": 239.96, \"end\": 253.0, \"text\": \"Zainab is the 7-year old Pakistani girl who was brutally raped, tortured and thrown into a pile of trash.\"}, {\"start\": 253.0, \"end\": 257.84, \"text\": \"A Pakistani government official claims they have found the DNA trace of the criminal involved\"}, {\"start\": 257.84, \"end\": 265.96, \"text\": \"in Zainab's case and he seems to be a serial killer.\"}, {\"start\": 265.96, \"end\": 271.72, \"text\": \"Eleven other girls have also been killed in recent weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 271.8, \"end\": 275.44, \"text\": \"Police say they've discovered DNA links between six of the murders.\"}, {\"start\": 275.44, \"end\": 280.08, \"text\": \"Police have taken some suspect into custody but they have not made an official arrest\"}, {\"start\": 280.08, \"end\": 283.04, \"text\": \"in the murders.\"}, {\"start\": 283.04, \"end\": 288.0, \"text\": \"Zainab's killing has angered local people who say the authorities have done too little\"}, {\"start\": 288.0, \"end\": 292.44, \"text\": \"to keep their children safe.\"}, {\"start\": 295.32, \"end\": 306.92, \"text\": \"Students at the University of Hawaii went into panic mode on Saturday after a false\"}, {\"start\": 306.92, \"end\": 308.48, \"text\": \"missile alert was issued.\"}, {\"start\": 308.48, \"end\": 315.2, \"text\": \"The alert went out on Saturday saying there was an inbound ballistic missile threat to\"}, {\"start\": 315.36, \"end\": 317.0, \"text\": \"the state.\"}, {\"start\": 317.0, \"end\": 328.96, \"text\": \"The message also told people to seek shelter right away and that it was not a drill.\"}, {\"start\": 328.96, \"end\": 341.52, \"text\": \"This is video of students running around campus in terror, scrambling for shelter.\"}, {\"start\": 341.52, \"end\": 347.96, \"text\": \"Some students could be heard yelling \\\"We gotta get out of here!\"}, {\"start\": 347.96, \"end\": 352.12, \"text\": \"We only have 15 minutes to get out of here!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 352.12, \"end\": 367.08, \"text\": \"However Govenor David Ige says that was an error caused by someone pushing the wrong\"}, {\"start\": 367.16, \"end\": 376.52, \"text\": \"button during a shift change.\"}, {\"start\": 376.52, \"end\": 387.16, \"text\": \"The second alert that clarified the threat was not real was sent out 38 minutes later.\"}, {\"start\": 387.16, \"end\": 393.92, \"text\": \"Hawaii's emergency management administrator is working to find out what went wrong in\"}, {\"start\": 393.92, \"end\": 399.12, \"text\": \"the agency's operation center.\"}, {\"start\": 401.16, \"end\": 423.12, \"text\": \"Earlier this week it was reported that actor Mark Wahlberg made a $1.5 million to reshoot\"}, {\"start\": 423.12, \"end\": 426.52, \"text\": \"scenes in the movie \\\"All The Money In The World.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 426.68, \"end\": 439.04, \"text\": \"His co-star Michelle Williams only received $1,000 per day.\"}, {\"start\": 439.04, \"end\": 451.84, \"text\": \"That caused a firestorm of debate about unequal pay for men versus women in Hollywood.\"}, {\"start\": 451.84, \"end\": 468.16, \"text\": \"Directors decided to reshoot scenes in the movie because actor Kevin Spacey was dropped\"}, {\"start\": 468.16, \"end\": 472.2, \"text\": \"from the film after several men accused him of sexual harassment and assault.\"}, {\"start\": 472.2, \"end\": 481.24, \"text\": \"Actor Christopher Plummer replaced Spacey in the movie.\"}, {\"start\": 481.24, \"end\": 494.28, \"text\": \"Later it was discovered Wahlberg's contract gave him \\\"co-star approval\\\" rights, which\"}, {\"start\": 494.28, \"end\": 509.68, \"text\": \"means Wahlberg would not approve the casting of Plummer unless he was paid $1.5 million.\"}, {\"start\": 509.68, \"end\": 517.32, \"text\": \"Williams did not have the same contract agreement.\"}, {\"start\": 517.32, \"end\": 519.72, \"text\": \"Now there's a new development.\"}, {\"start\": 519.72, \"end\": 533.24, \"text\": \"According to Variety magazine, Wahlberg is now donating all of his reshoot money, $1.5\"}, {\"start\": 533.24, \"end\": 547.48, \"text\": \"million, to the Times Up legal defense fund and he's adding another 500,000 to the fund.\"}, {\"start\": 547.48, \"end\": 563.04, \"text\": \"#TIMESUP is the movement in Hollywood to fight sexual harassment against women.\"}, {\"start\": 565.24, \"end\": 567.48, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 567.48, \"end\": 568.6, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 568.6, \"end\": 570.72, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 570.72, \"end\": 575.12, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 575.12, \"end\": 580.16, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "PRqdTNUduvE": {
    "video_id": "PRqdTNUduvE",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.21.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180422",
    "duration": 482,
    "view_count": 1732,
    "description": "4.21.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Police release mug shot of Ocala School shooter\n-Barbara Bush funeral\n-India pushes to change rape law\n-Kim Jong Un suspends nuclear tests\n-FAA orders new engine inspection requirements\n-\"Austin Powers\" actor Verne Troyer dead at 49\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUD",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.24, \"end\": 9.66, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.66, \"end\": 11.76, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.76, \"end\": 12.98, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.08, \"end\": 16.24, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.14, \"end\": 30.66, \"text\": \"Police in Ocala, Florida have released the mug shot of 19-year-old Sky Bouche.\"}, {\"start\": 30.7, \"end\": 37.08, \"text\": \"He's accused of shooting at students at Forest high school on Friday just before the students\"}, {\"start\": 37.08, \"end\": 48.7, \"text\": \"were scheduled to walk out as part of a national protest against gun violence.\"}, {\"start\": 48.7, \"end\": 51.16, \"text\": \"One student was wounded.\"}, {\"start\": 51.16, \"end\": 61.68, \"text\": \"As Bouche was being escorted into police headquarters, several reporters asked him whether he had\"}, {\"start\": 61.68, \"end\": 64.48, \"text\": \"anything to say.\"}, {\"start\": 64.48, \"end\": 71.46, \"text\": \"Bouche responded: \\\"I'm sorry. It doesn't make it better anyway.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 71.46, \"end\": 84.88, \"text\": \"He is facing a long list of charges including terrorism, aggravated assault with a firearm\"}, {\"start\": 84.98, \"end\": 88.54, \"text\": \"and possessing a firearm on school property.\"}, {\"start\": 91.66, \"end\": 100.9, \"text\": \"About 1,500 mourners were at the funeral of former First Lady Barbara Bush today.\"}, {\"start\": 100.9, \"end\": 107.84, \"text\": \"It was an \\\"invitation-only\\\" service and a simple one, at her request.\"}, {\"start\": 107.98, \"end\": 125.14, \"text\": \"Former Presidents Barack Obama, Bill Clinton and their wives attended the service.\"}, {\"start\": 125.14, \"end\": 131.28, \"text\": \"First Lady Melania Trump was also in attendance.\"}, {\"start\": 131.28, \"end\": 142.88, \"text\": \"Many of the women wore strands of pearls which were a favorite accessory for Barbara Bush.\"}, {\"start\": 142.88, \"end\": 154.08, \"text\": \"President Trump decided not to attend to avoid disruptions and to respect the Bush family.\"}, {\"start\": 154.08, \"end\": 163.68, \"text\": \"But he did send a tweet which said he would be watching the funeral from his resort in\"}, {\"start\": 163.68, \"end\": 170.4, \"text\": \"Mar-A-Lago.\"}, {\"start\": 170.44, \"end\": 179.64, \"text\": \"It's not unusual for a sitting president to miss a funeral.\"}, {\"start\": 179.64, \"end\": 195.06, \"text\": \"Obama didn't attend Nancy Reagan's funeral in 2016 and George W. Bush did not attend\"}, {\"start\": 195.06, \"end\": 200.58, \"text\": \"Lady Bird Johnson's funeral in 2007.\"}, {\"start\": 204.58, \"end\": 213.84, \"text\": \"India's lawmakers have passed an executive order to make the rape of a girl under 12\"}, {\"start\": 213.84, \"end\": 216.4, \"text\": \"punishable by the death penalty.\"}, {\"start\": 216.4, \"end\": 227.0, \"text\": \"The new order is a result of national outrage over brutal sexual violence in the country\"}, {\"start\": 227.0, \"end\": 230.0, \"text\": \"in the past few months.\"}, {\"start\": 230.0, \"end\": 239.06, \"text\": \"The order will also increase the minimum punishment for female rape from 7 years to 10 years,\"}, {\"start\": 239.18, \"end\": 242.84, \"text\": \"which can be extended to life in prison.\"}, {\"start\": 242.84, \"end\": 250.06, \"text\": \"The change in law will become permanent once it is approved by India's Parliament then\"}, {\"start\": 250.06, \"end\": 255.34, \"text\": \"signed by the president.\"}, {\"start\": 257.76, \"end\": 269.08, \"text\": \"Today North Korea's leader Kim Jong Un announced the government no longer needs nuclear or\"}, {\"start\": 269.08, \"end\": 272.76, \"text\": \"ballistic missile tests.\"}, {\"start\": 272.76, \"end\": 281.28, \"text\": \"This is a stunning reversal from last year when Kim Jong-Un aggressively announced and\"}, {\"start\": 281.28, \"end\": 288.24, \"text\": \"demonstrated his country's nuclear testing ability.\"}, {\"start\": 288.24, \"end\": 294.38, \"text\": \"Today's announcement comes just before next week's historic meeting between Kim Jong-Un\"}, {\"start\": 294.38, \"end\": 313.58, \"text\": \"and South Korean President Moon Jae-In and a potential meeting with President Trump after that.\"}, {\"start\": 318.32, \"end\": 329.94, \"text\": \"The Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) is ordering all airlines to inspect engines\"}, {\"start\": 329.94, \"end\": 335.5, \"text\": \"similar to the one that killed a woman in midflight Tuesday when a fan blade broke off.\"}, {\"start\": 335.5, \"end\": 346.38, \"text\": \"FAA officials say the naked eye cannot detect the cracks and signs of metal fatigue that\"}, {\"start\": 346.38, \"end\": 361.0, \"text\": \"led to Tuesday's accident so airlines must use ultrasound technology to inspect the engines.\"}, {\"start\": 361.0, \"end\": 367.34, \"text\": \"Airlines have 20 days to perform the inspections.\"}, {\"start\": 367.34, \"end\": 375.58, \"text\": \"The inspections can be done while the engine is mounted to the plane's wings and each is\"}, {\"start\": 375.58, \"end\": 380.28, \"text\": \"expected to take 2 to 4 hours.\"}, {\"start\": 383.32, \"end\": 399.8, \"text\": \"Verne Troyer, the actor best known for playing \\\"Mini Me\\\" in the Austin Powers films, has died.\"}, {\"start\": 399.86, \"end\": 407.0, \"text\": \"Troyer's death was announced Saturday in a statement on the actor's Facebook page.\"}, {\"start\": 407.0, \"end\": 419.48, \"text\": \"A cause of death was not revealed but the statement mentioned that Troyer had been dealing\"}, {\"start\": 419.48, \"end\": 428.22, \"text\": \"with a, quote, \\\"recent time of adversity.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 428.22, \"end\": 438.28, \"text\": \"Troyer was one of the shortest people in the world, standing just 2 feet, 8 inches tall\"}, {\"start\": 438.28, \"end\": 444.78, \"text\": \"but he achieved success as an actor, appearing in more than two dozen films.\"}, {\"start\": 444.78, \"end\": 449.44, \"text\": \"Verne Troyer was 49 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 452.82, \"end\": 455.6, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 455.6, \"end\": 457.02, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 457.02, \"end\": 461.14, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 461.14, \"end\": 467.64, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 467.72, \"end\": 470.56, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 470.56, \"end\": 472.32, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 472.32, \"end\": 475.64, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "y57lszB5Ptk": {
    "video_id": "y57lszB5Ptk",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.22.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180423",
    "duration": 602,
    "view_count": 2048,
    "description": "4.22.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Half naked gunman kills four at Nashville Waffle House\n-Bush office shares photos from Barbara Bush funeral\n-Musical memorial pays tribute to beloved DJ Avicii\n-Michael Jackson's moonwalk shoes up for auction\n-Weekend box office\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET U",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.54, \"end\": 9.06, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.06, \"end\": 10.92, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.92, \"end\": 12.36, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.36, \"end\": 15.76, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.48, \"end\": 25.22, \"text\": \"A massive search effort is underway for this man.\"}, {\"start\": 25.22, \"end\": 33.14, \"text\": \"Police in Nashville, Tennessee say at about 3:25 Sunday morning Central Time, 29-year-old\"}, {\"start\": 33.26, \"end\": 45.44, \"text\": \"Travis Reinking from Illinois walked into Waffle House wearing nothing but a jacket\"}, {\"start\": 45.44, \"end\": 47.86, \"text\": \"and open fire.\"}, {\"start\": 47.86, \"end\": 57.12, \"text\": \"Witnesses say they saw him sitting in his truck outside the restaurant for a few minutes.\"}, {\"start\": 57.12, \"end\": 62.48, \"text\": \"When he got out, witnesses to say he shot and killed two people outside the restaurant,\"}, {\"start\": 62.48, \"end\": 66.26, \"text\": \"then walked inside and killed two more people.\"}, {\"start\": 66.26, \"end\": 68.56, \"text\": \"At least four people were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 68.56, \"end\": 78.22, \"text\": \"Police say the shooting would have continued were it not for the heroics of one customer.\"}, {\"start\": 78.22, \"end\": 87.38, \"text\": \"James Shaw Junior hid near the restaurant's bathroom and when he saw Reinking fidgeting\"}, {\"start\": 87.38, \"end\": 96.38, \"text\": \"with his AR-15 rifle, he jumped into action and wrestled the rifle away from Reinking.\"}, {\"start\": 96.38, \"end\": 99.08, \"text\": \"Reinking fled the restaurant.\"}, {\"start\": 99.08, \"end\": 105.1, \"text\": \"Police later found the jacket Reinking was wearing about a block away.\"}, {\"start\": 105.1, \"end\": 114.58, \"text\": \"Inside the jacket, investigators found two magazines for the AR-15 rifle, leading them\"}, {\"start\": 114.58, \"end\": 118.24, \"text\": \"to believe if Shaw had not intervened, the carnage from the shooting would have been\"}, {\"start\": 118.24, \"end\": 120.6, \"text\": \"much worse.\"}, {\"start\": 120.6, \"end\": 127.24, \"text\": \"Nashville police are asking residents to lock their doors and to call police immediately\"}, {\"start\": 127.26, \"end\": 129.86, \"text\": \"if they see Reinking.\"}, {\"start\": 129.86, \"end\": 138.06, \"text\": \"After searching his apartment, SWAT team members realized there were two more guns licensed\"}, {\"start\": 138.06, \"end\": 144.1, \"text\": \"to Reinking that are unaccounted for, a hunting rifle and a handgun, which means he may still\"}, {\"start\": 144.1, \"end\": 147.72, \"text\": \"be armed.\"}, {\"start\": 147.72, \"end\": 158.36, \"text\": \"If you see Reinking you are urged to call Nashville police at 615-862-8600 or\"}, {\"start\": 158.36, \"end\": 161.36, \"text\": \"your local FBI office.\"}, {\"start\": 165.46, \"end\": 174.92, \"text\": \"The office of former President George H.W. Bush has released some unique photos from\"}, {\"start\": 174.92, \"end\": 180.22, \"text\": \"Barbara Bush's funeral.\"}, {\"start\": 180.22, \"end\": 188.74, \"text\": \"One set shows an array of high profile political figures together paying their respects near\"}, {\"start\": 188.74, \"end\": 191.84, \"text\": \"Mrs. Bush's casket.\"}, {\"start\": 191.84, \"end\": 212.18, \"text\": \"Posing with current First Lady Melania Trump were the elder Bush, his son, former President\"}, {\"start\": 212.18, \"end\": 232.76, \"text\": \"George W. Bush, former President Barack Obama and former first lady Michelle Obama and former\"}, {\"start\": 232.76, \"end\": 247.339, \"text\": \"President Bill Clinton with former Secretary of State and former first lady Hillary Clinton.\"}, {\"start\": 247.34, \"end\": 257.14, \"text\": \"The second set of photos are from the George H.W. Bush library in College Station, where\"}, {\"start\": 257.14, \"end\": 262.58, \"text\": \"Mrs. Bush is buried.\"}, {\"start\": 262.58, \"end\": 270.82, \"text\": \"They show the casket being carried and the interment ceremony.\"}, {\"start\": 270.82, \"end\": 280.26, \"text\": \"More than 1,000 people gathered to mourn the former first lady at her funeral Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 280.26, \"end\": 284.02, \"text\": \"She passed away Tuesday at the age of 92.\"}, {\"start\": 288.16, \"end\": 300.54, \"text\": \"Thousands of fans gathered in Stockholm, Sweden to sing, dance and listen to the music of\"}, {\"start\": 300.54, \"end\": 308.26, \"text\": \"famous DJ and musician Tim \\\"Avicii\\\" Bergling.\"}, {\"start\": 308.26, \"end\": 314.96, \"text\": \"Avicii died suddenly at the age of 28 while on vacation with friends in Oman.\"}, {\"start\": 314.96, \"end\": 323.76, \"text\": \"Oman police say they have conducted two examinations of Avicii's body and see no signs of foul play.\"}, {\"start\": 323.92, \"end\": 328.24, \"text\": \"But no cause of death has been given yet.\"}, {\"start\": 328.24, \"end\": 337.36, \"text\": \"Avicii's music spanned all social and cultural lines as was evidenced by the people that\"}, {\"start\": 337.36, \"end\": 341.66, \"text\": \"showed up for the musical memorial.\"}, {\"start\": 341.74, \"end\": 350.2, \"text\": \"The crowd was made up of Swedish royals, artists, politicians and the general public.\"}, {\"start\": 350.2, \"end\": 356.88, \"text\": \"Avicii was a big name in the electronic dance music genre known as EDM.\"}, {\"start\": 356.88, \"end\": 372.48, \"text\": \"He worked with artists such as Madonna and Chris Martin and had a crossover pop hit in\"}, {\"start\": 372.48, \"end\": 379.599, \"text\": \"2013 entitled \\\"Wake Me Up.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 379.6, \"end\": 392.34, \"text\": \"But he constantly struggled with his fame and two years ago, he walked away from the limelight,\"}, {\"start\": 392.34, \"end\": 400.02, \"text\": \"saying the stress, anxiety and health issues associated with excessive drinking were taking\"}, {\"start\": 400.02, \"end\": 403.6, \"text\": \"its toll on him.\"}, {\"start\": 406.18, \"end\": 420.68, \"text\": \"The shoes worn by Michael Jackson when he performed his signature \\\"moonwalk\\\" for the\"}, {\"start\": 420.78, \"end\": 422.34, \"text\": \"first time on stage are going up for auction.\"}, {\"start\": 422.34, \"end\": 433.33, \"text\": \"The \\\"King of Pop\\\" wore the black loafers during rehearsals for the \\\"Motown 25\\\" TV special\"}, {\"start\": 433.33, \"end\": 435.5, \"text\": \"in 1983.\"}, {\"start\": 435.5, \"end\": 443.72, \"text\": \"GSW Auctions will sell the leather shoes at a live auction on May 26.\"}, {\"start\": 443.72, \"end\": 450.14, \"text\": \"They estimate that the loafers will sell for around $10,000.\"}, {\"start\": 450.14, \"end\": 459.88, \"text\": \"The auction house said Jackson gave the shoes to a dancer-choreographer after the rehearsal\"}, {\"start\": 459.88, \"end\": 461.92, \"text\": \"and that owner has had them ever since.\"}, {\"start\": 461.92, \"end\": 471.24, \"text\": \"Jackson's performance of \\\"Billie Jean\\\" for that \\\"Motown 25\\\" special marked the debut\"}, {\"start\": 471.24, \"end\": 477.56, \"text\": \"of the backward sliding dance known as the \\\"moonwalk.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 479.8, \"end\": 490.9, \"text\": \"\\\"A Quiet Place\\\" is back on top in the weekend box office.\"}, {\"start\": 490.9, \"end\": 509.28, \"text\": \"The thriller starring young deaf actress Millicent Simmonds grossed $22 million in its third week.\"}, {\"start\": 509.28, \"end\": 517.08, \"text\": \"I've already seen it and it is simply phenomenal!\"}, {\"start\": 517.08, \"end\": 523.2, \"text\": \"Actually I've seen it twice and I, most likely, will go back a third time.\"}, {\"start\": 523.2, \"end\": 539.36, \"text\": \"Dwayne \\\"The Rock\\\" Johnson's fantasy/sci-fi film \\\"Rampage\\\" followed closely behind with\"}, {\"start\": 539.36, \"end\": 543.32, \"text\": \"$21 million.\"}, {\"start\": 543.36, \"end\": 553.04, \"text\": \"Interesting side note: Johnson's character Davis uses basic sign language to communicate\"}, {\"start\": 553.04, \"end\": 557.36, \"text\": \"with George the gorilla.\"}, {\"start\": 557.36, \"end\": 575.12, \"text\": \"In third place, Amy Schumer's comedy flick \\\"I Feel Pretty\\\" debuted with $16.2 million.\"}, {\"start\": 578.56, \"end\": 580.58, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 580.58, \"end\": 582.1, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 582.1, \"end\": 584.12, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 584.12, \"end\": 588.48, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 588.48, \"end\": 589.64, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 589.64, \"end\": 590.88, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 590.88, \"end\": 594.24, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "Zqu4yvHmSmI": {
    "video_id": "Zqu4yvHmSmI",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.30.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171231",
    "duration": 721,
    "view_count": 1138,
    "description": "December 30, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-A LOOK INSIDE BURNED BRONX APARTMENT BUILDING\n-\"REAL HOUSEWIVES\" STAR ENTERS REHAB\n-ACTIVIST ERICA GARNER DEAD AT 27 YEARS OLD\n-POLITICIANS AND THE CURSE OF THE PANDA\n-WIDESPREAD FLU CASES REPORTED IN 36 STATES\n-STORIES THAT DEFINED 2017\n-GET READY TO RING IN A FRIGID NEW YEAR\n-BUBBLE FREEZES IN THE COLD\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.84, \"end\": 6.66, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.66, \"end\": 8.26, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.26, \"end\": 9.34, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 9.34, \"end\": 11.76, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 13.74, \"end\": 19.88, \"text\": \"We're now getting a look inside the Bronx apartment building that was destroyed by fire\"}, {\"start\": 19.88, \"end\": 21.22, \"text\": \"Thursday night.\"}, {\"start\": 21.22, \"end\": 24.82, \"text\": \"12 people were killed, including three children.\"}, {\"start\": 24.82, \"end\": 27.88, \"text\": \"7 firefighters were also injured.\"}, {\"start\": 27.88, \"end\": 33.8, \"text\": \"NYPD says they are still working to identify all of the victims.\"}, {\"start\": 33.84, \"end\": 41.12, \"text\": \"Officials say the flames started in a first floor unit, where a three-year-old boy was\"}, {\"start\": 41.12, \"end\": 43.84, \"text\": \"playing with the burners on the stove.\"}, {\"start\": 43.84, \"end\": 48.04, \"text\": \"When his mother rushed out of her apartment, she left the door open and that cause flames\"}, {\"start\": 48.2, \"end\": 51.48, \"text\": \"to quickly spread up the stairs to other floors.\"}, {\"start\": 51.48, \"end\": 59.0, \"text\": \"The city fire commissioner reminded all residents that in a fire emergency, closing all doors\"}, {\"start\": 59.08, \"end\": 68.08, \"text\": \"is a critical step to help prevent tragedies like this.\"}, {\"start\": 70.36, \"end\": 80.64, \"text\": \"In the early morning hours of Christmas Eve, \\\"Real Housewives of New York\\\" star Luann de\"}, {\"start\": 80.64, \"end\": 84.52, \"text\": \"Lesseps was arrested in Palm Beach, Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 84.52, \"end\": 90.96, \"text\": \"She was charged with battery of an officer, resisting arrest and disorderly intoxication.\"}, {\"start\": 90.96, \"end\": 94.88, \"text\": \"Now de Lesseps is apologizing and says she's headed for rehab.\"}, {\"start\": 94.88, \"end\": 97.4, \"text\": \"On social media she said she was truly embarrassed.\"}, {\"start\": 97.4, \"end\": 104.6, \"text\": \"She apologized for her actions and said they do not reflect her core values.\"}, {\"start\": 104.6, \"end\": 109.8, \"text\": \"De Lesseps went on to say she will voluntarily check into an alcohol treatment center.\"}, {\"start\": 109.8, \"end\": 116.44, \"text\": \"She also said being Palm Beach brought up long-buried emotions since her second marriage\"}, {\"start\": 116.44, \"end\": 118.76, \"text\": \"there.\"}, {\"start\": 118.76, \"end\": 125.84, \"text\": \"That union with Tom D'Agostino Junior ended in August.\"}, {\"start\": 129.32, \"end\": 139.28, \"text\": \"Erica Garner, an activist for social justice, died on Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 139.32, \"end\": 144.56, \"text\": \"Last week she suffered a massive heart attack and was left with severe brain damage.\"}, {\"start\": 144.56, \"end\": 146.64, \"text\": \"She was 27 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 146.64, \"end\": 153.0, \"text\": \"Garner was the oldest daughter of Eric Garner.\"}, {\"start\": 153.0, \"end\": 158.0, \"text\": \"In 2014, police tried to arrest him for selling cigarettes illegally.\"}, {\"start\": 158.0, \"end\": 162.56, \"text\": \"Video of the incident showed police tackling him from behind and taking him to the ground\"}, {\"start\": 162.56, \"end\": 169.64, \"text\": \"using a chokehold, a move that was banned by NYPD.\"}, {\"start\": 169.64, \"end\": 171.8, \"text\": \"Eric Garner, who had asthma, died that day.\"}, {\"start\": 171.8, \"end\": 173.04, \"text\": \"His last words \\\"I can't breathe!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 173.04, \"end\": 188.72, \"text\": \"\\\"I can't breathe!\\\" became a rallying cry for protesters and sparked the \\\"Black Lives Matter\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 188.88, \"end\": 190.76, \"text\": \"movement.\"}, {\"start\": 190.92, \"end\": 199.16, \"text\": \"Erica Garner became a prominent social and political activist after her father's death,\"}, {\"start\": 199.16, \"end\": 202.92, \"text\": \"speaking out against police brutality.\"}, {\"start\": 205.72, \"end\": 212.64, \"text\": \"According to declassified papers released by the UK national archives,\"}, {\"start\": 212.64, \"end\": 227.04, \"text\": \"back in 1981 a panda missed out on a first-class flight to Washington because Prime Minister\"}, {\"start\": 227.04, \"end\": 229.04, \"text\": \"Margaret Thatcher refused to let it ride on the plane with her.\"}, {\"start\": 229.04, \"end\": 233.44, \"text\": \"She said panders are bad omens for politicians.\"}, {\"start\": 233.48, \"end\": 235.92, \"text\": \"And she may have been right.\"}, {\"start\": 235.92, \"end\": 247.16, \"text\": \"Did you know Japan's Prime Minister Kakuei Tanaka was given two pandas in 1971.\"}, {\"start\": 247.16, \"end\": 250.0, \"text\": \"Three years later he resigned.\"}, {\"start\": 250.04, \"end\": 257.96, \"text\": \"Two pandas were also given to US President Richard Nixon in 1972.\"}, {\"start\": 257.96, \"end\": 262.0, \"text\": \"Within two years, he became the first American president to resign.\"}, {\"start\": 262.08, \"end\": 271.68, \"text\": \"In 1973 two pandas were given to France's president Georges Pompidou.\"}, {\"start\": 271.68, \"end\": 274.28, \"text\": \"He died a year later.\"}, {\"start\": 274.28, \"end\": 281.56, \"text\": \"Then there was Thatcher's own predecessor, British Prime Minister Ted Heath.\"}, {\"start\": 281.56, \"end\": 284.12, \"text\": \"He was also given a pair of pandas.\"}, {\"start\": 284.12, \"end\": 287.12, \"text\": \"Not long after that, he lost an election.\"}, {\"start\": 287.12, \"end\": 298.48, \"text\": \"German Chancellor Angela Merkel unveil pandas at the Berlin zoo this summer.\"}, {\"start\": 298.48, \"end\": 302.2, \"text\": \"Weeks later she failed to win a majority in the election.\"}, {\"start\": 302.2, \"end\": 317.04, \"text\": \"So perhaps is no surprise that President Trump left China before First Lady Melania Trump\"}, {\"start\": 317.04, \"end\": 320.2, \"text\": \"paid a visit to Beijing's panda zoo earlier this year.\"}, {\"start\": 322.16, \"end\": 326.36, \"text\": \"Flu season is in full swing across the US.\"}, {\"start\": 326.36, \"end\": 334.28, \"text\": \"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention reported a sharp increase of influenza activity\"}, {\"start\": 334.28, \"end\": 335.88, \"text\": \"last week.\"}, {\"start\": 335.88, \"end\": 339.2, \"text\": \"It was widespread in 36 states.\"}, {\"start\": 339.2, \"end\": 347.6, \"text\": \"The CDC also says 12 children have died from the flu this season and more than 2,400 people\"}, {\"start\": 347.68, \"end\": 349.4, \"text\": \"hospitalized.\"}, {\"start\": 349.4, \"end\": 359.08, \"text\": \"Experts believe the flu virus is spread when a sick person talks, sneezes or coughs.\"}, {\"start\": 359.08, \"end\": 373.04, \"text\": \"Common symptoms include fever, chills, cough, sore throat, headaches and fatigue.\"}, {\"start\": 373.04, \"end\": 378.64, \"text\": \"Despite these painful symptoms, most people recover in less than two weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 381.6, \"end\": 390.68, \"text\": \"Without a doubt, 2017 has been a turbulent year.\"}, {\"start\": 390.68, \"end\": 400.68, \"text\": \"There have been controversies, conflicts, chaos and social and political change.\"}, {\"start\": 400.68, \"end\": 405.96, \"text\": \"Here's a quick recap of the stories that defined 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 405.96, \"end\": 415.2, \"text\": \"Number one: Donald Trump was elected president, a president unlike any we've ever seen before.\"}, {\"start\": 415.2, \"end\": 423.64, \"text\": \"He has become famous for his controversies, name-calling and internal battles.\"}, {\"start\": 423.64, \"end\": 431.32, \"text\": \"Number two: a slew of terror attacks hit at the heart of cities around the world.\"}, {\"start\": 431.32, \"end\": 438.28, \"text\": \"The UK suffered the highest number of attacks and New York City experienced its deadliest\"}, {\"start\": 438.28, \"end\": 441.6, \"text\": \"terror attacks since 9/11.\"}, {\"start\": 441.6, \"end\": 449.12, \"text\": \"The US suffered some of the deadliest mass shootings in its modern history.\"}, {\"start\": 449.12, \"end\": 458.76, \"text\": \"The world experienced a mind-bending litany of natural disasters.\"}, {\"start\": 458.76, \"end\": 470.96, \"text\": \"And CNN exposed slave auctions in Libya, sparking outrage around the world and prompting investigations.\"}, {\"start\": 470.96, \"end\": 476.6, \"text\": \"But away from the darkness, there was some light.\"}, {\"start\": 476.6, \"end\": 487.6, \"text\": \"Millions of women across the globe spoke out against sexual harassment.\"}, {\"start\": 487.6, \"end\": 497.24, \"text\": \"Astronomers found new planets.\"}, {\"start\": 497.24, \"end\": 503.04, \"text\": \"Australia voted \\\"yes\\\" to same-sex marriage.\"}, {\"start\": 503.04, \"end\": 520.0, \"text\": \"An epic mixup at the Oscars went viral.\"}, {\"start\": 520.0, \"end\": 524.88, \"text\": \"A royal wedding was confirmed.\"}, {\"start\": 524.88, \"end\": 533.48, \"text\": \"And America got to see its first nationwide solar eclipse in 99 years.\"}, {\"start\": 536.0, \"end\": 553.2, \"text\": \"If you plan on counting down to 2018 outdoors on Sunday night, be prepared to wrap up.\"}, {\"start\": 553.2, \"end\": 566.44, \"text\": \"Weather forecasts for New Year's predict it's going to be 20 to 40 degrees colder than usual\"}, {\"start\": 566.44, \"end\": 568.64, \"text\": \"for many parts of the US.\"}, {\"start\": 568.64, \"end\": 575.32, \"text\": \"That's because arctic air is blasting over the Northeast, dropping temperatures drastically\"}, {\"start\": 575.32, \"end\": 580.64, \"text\": \"from New England to Texas.\"}, {\"start\": 580.64, \"end\": 587.96, \"text\": \"Minneapolis can expect temperatures to drop to a low of -13 degrees.\"}, {\"start\": 587.96, \"end\": 593.0, \"text\": \"Chicago could see a bone chilling -15 degrees on New Year's Eve.\"}, {\"start\": 593.0, \"end\": 601.12, \"text\": \"If you're thinking of going to Times Square in New York City to watch the ball drop, the\"}, {\"start\": 601.12, \"end\": 607.78, \"text\": \"wind chill is expected to drop to zero, which would make this the third coldest ball drop\"}, {\"start\": 607.78, \"end\": 610.42, \"text\": \"ever.\"}, {\"start\": 612.84, \"end\": 620.0, \"text\": \"A woman in Columbus, Ohio shared a spectacular video.\"}, {\"start\": 620.0, \"end\": 627.2, \"text\": \"It shows a bubble freezing right in front of your eyes.\"}, {\"start\": 627.2, \"end\": 632.76, \"text\": \"She says she did not use any special effects.\"}, {\"start\": 632.76, \"end\": 635.96, \"text\": \"She just let mother nature do all the work.\"}, {\"start\": 636.0, \"end\": 637.28, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 670.84, \"end\": 680.94, \"text\": \"If you want to try this yourself, the woman says take a cup of water and mix in 2 tablespoons\"}, {\"start\": 680.94, \"end\": 691.92, \"text\": \"each of dish soap, corn syrup and regular sugar.\"}, {\"start\": 691.92, \"end\": 698.94, \"text\": \"Of course it has to be below freezing outside in order for it to work.\"}, {\"start\": 700.56, \"end\": 702.64, \"text\": \"And those your top stories.\"}, {\"start\": 702.64, \"end\": 703.88, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 703.92, \"end\": 706.16, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 706.16, \"end\": 709.6, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 709.6, \"end\": 714.82, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "V0VAETm1R4E": {
    "video_id": "V0VAETm1R4E",
    "title": "Sign1News anchor Candace Jones signs National Anthem (ASL - 3.18.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180319",
    "duration": 150,
    "view_count": 231,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.42, \"end\": 12.06, \"text\": \"We want to congratulate Sign1News anchor Candace Jones!\"}, {\"start\": 12.06, \"end\": 25.16, \"text\": \"She stood in front of 60,000 soccer fans and signed the US and Canadian national anthem\"}, {\"start\": 25.16, \"end\": 45.02, \"text\": \"at the Atlanta United-Vancouver Whitecaps game Saturday night at Mercedes-Benz Stadium.\"}, {\"start\": 45.02, \"end\": 56.44, \"text\": \"Some team officials say her rendition was one of the best interpretations they've ever seen.\"}, {\"start\": 56.44, \"end\": 65.16, \"text\": \"Jones said she was a little nervous before she started but really got into it once the\"}, {\"start\": 65.16, \"end\": 69.62, \"text\": \"song started.\"}, {\"start\": 69.62, \"end\": 78.22, \"text\": \"Afterwards she said she was honored to be a role model for the Deaf community, especially\"}, {\"start\": 78.22, \"end\": 80.3, \"text\": \"for young people.\"}, {\"start\": 82.74, \"end\": 86.52, \"text\": \"It feels wonderful to be a role model for the deaf community and to show the hearing\"}, {\"start\": 86.52, \"end\": 91.74, \"text\": \"world that Deaf people can interpret music even if they can't hear the words.\"}, {\"start\": 91.74, \"end\": 96.04, \"text\": \"They see how we express music through signs and facial expressions.\"}, {\"start\": 96.04, \"end\": 102.16, \"text\": \"This week my students told me they were going to watch the Atlanta United game with their families.\"}, {\"start\": 102.16, \"end\": 105.92, \"text\": \"When I told them I was going to be at the game signing the national anthem, they were\"}, {\"start\": 105.92, \"end\": 109.64, \"text\": \"so excited!\"}, {\"start\": 109.64, \"end\": 114.8, \"text\": \"So instead of just watching someone singing the national anthem, they actually got to\"}, {\"start\": 114.8, \"end\": 120.64, \"text\": \"see someone, me, their teacher, signing in their language.\"}, {\"start\": 120.64, \"end\": 122.64, \"text\": \"It was fabulous!\"}, {\"start\": 124.24, \"end\": 130.84, \"text\": \"Jones may have been the team's good luck charm too.\"}, {\"start\": 130.84, \"end\": 134.76, \"text\": \"Atlanta beat Vancouver 4-1.\"}, {\"start\": 134.76, \"end\": 141.52, \"text\": \"If you missed Jones' performance, you can see it in its entirety on our Facebook page\"}, {\"start\": 141.68, \"end\": 145.88, \"text\": \"as well as behind-the-scenes footage.\"}, {\"start\": 145.88, \"end\": 148.36, \"text\": \"Again congratulations Candace.\"}]"
  },
  "HOfd4HntEt4": {
    "video_id": "HOfd4HntEt4",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.7.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171108",
    "duration": 493,
    "view_count": 121,
    "description": "November 7, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-TEXAS CHURCH SHOOTING UPDATE\n-TX SHOOTER POSTED PICS OF RIFLE ON FACEBOOK\n-PRO AND ANTI TRUMP RALLIES IN SOUTH KOREA\n-INVESTIGATION LAUNCHED INTO DEATH OF 26 MIGRANTS\n-PRINCE GUITAR SOLD FOR $700K AT AUCTION\n-TWITTER EXPANDS 280-CHARACTER LIMIT\n-IPHONE BUG WON’T LET USERS TYPE “I”\n-DOG EATS IN HIGH CHAIR\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 10.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.024, \"end\": 15.024, \"text\": \"I am Jethro Wooddall and here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.1, \"end\": 21.1, \"text\": \"The front lawn of First Baptist Church in Sutherland Springs, Texas has\"}, {\"start\": 22.0, \"end\": 27.0, \"text\": \"turned into a memorial to honor the\"}, {\"start\": 27.0, \"end\": 32.0, \"text\": \"26 people killed on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 33.0, \"end\": 38.0, \"text\": \"We have learned that the families of the deceased victims will not be\"}, {\"start\": 38.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"burdened with the financial cost of burying their loved ones.\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 48.0, \"text\": \"According to the Wilson County district attorney each family will get enough money to\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 52.0, \"text\": \"cover funeral expenses through the crime victim compensation\"}, {\"start\": 52.0, \"end\": 60.0, \"text\": \"fund. The amount for each victim is $6500.\"}, {\"start\": 61.0, \"end\": 66.0, \"text\": \"The D.A. also said a company has agreed to donate the\"}, {\"start\": 66.0, \"end\": 68.0, \"text\": \"caskets for all of the victims.\"}, {\"start\": 71.0, \"end\": 76.0, \"text\": \"A week before the Texas church shooting attacker Devin\"}, {\"start\": 76.0, \"end\": 80.0, \"text\": \"Kelley posted a picture of a rifle on Facebook.\"}, {\"start\": 80.0, \"end\": 86.0, \"text\": \"Preliminary reports indicate that Kelley used a semi-automatic\"}, {\"start\": 86.0, \"end\": 90.0, \"text\": \"weapon and authorities say they recovered\"}, {\"start\": 90.0, \"end\": 95.0, \"text\": \"a Ruger 556 rifle at the scene.\"}, {\"start\": 96.0, \"end\": 100.0, \"text\": \"It's not clear whether the rifle in the picture is the same gun as the\"}, {\"start\": 100.0, \"end\": 105.0, \"text\": \"one used in the massacre. Kelley was later found in his car\"}, {\"start\": 105.0, \"end\": 110.0, \"text\": \"a few miles away with a self-inflicted gunshot wound to the head.\"}, {\"start\": 111.0, \"end\": 115.0, \"text\": \"A law enforcement official says Kelley bought the rifle in April of\"}, {\"start\": 115.0, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"2016. He says when Kelley filled out the background\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 125.0, \"text\": \"check he did not check the box indicating he had a\"}, {\"start\": 125.0, \"end\": 130.0, \"text\": \"disqualifying criminal history.\"}, {\"start\": 130.0, \"end\": 134.0, \"text\": \"There are records he also purchased three other weapons\"}, {\"start\": 135.0, \"end\": 140.0, \"text\": \"between 2014 and this year. And the Air Force\"}, {\"start\": 140.0, \"end\": 145.0, \"text\": \"has admitted it failed to alert law enforcement about\"}, {\"start\": 145.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"Kelley's violent past -- which could have prevented him\"}, {\"start\": 150.0, \"end\": 155.0, \"text\": \"from buying the gun he purchased in 2016\"}, {\"start\": 155.0, \"end\": 161.0, \"text\": \"and the one he used on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 163.0, \"end\": 168.0, \"text\": \"President Trump's visit to South Korea has already\"}, {\"start\": 168.0, \"end\": 173.0, \"text\": \"proved polarizing. There were pro-Trump supporters on one\"}, {\"start\": 173.0, \"end\": 179.0, \"text\": \"side of the street and anti-Trump protesters on the other.\"}, {\"start\": 179.0, \"end\": 184.0, \"text\": \"Authorities say about 5,000 people showed up in\"}, {\"start\": 184.0, \"end\": 189.0, \"text\": \"downtown Seoul. The anti-Trump crowd was\"}, {\"start\": 189.0, \"end\": 193.0, \"text\": \"much bigger than the pro-Trump crowd.\"}, {\"start\": 193.0, \"end\": 198.0, \"text\": \"Anti-Trump protesters believe that Trump has made it more tense in the\"}, {\"start\": 198.0, \"end\": 203.0, \"text\": \"region because of his heated words about North Korea and its leader\"}, {\"start\": 203.0, \"end\": 208.0, \"text\": \"Kim Jong Un. Many were chanting\"}, {\"start\": 208.0, \"end\": 213.0, \"text\": \"\\\"No Trump, no war!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 213.0, \"end\": 218.0, \"text\": \"On the other side of the road pro-Turmp supporters wanted the president to know he was\"}, {\"start\": 218.0, \"end\": 220.0, \"text\": \"welcome in South Korea.\"}, {\"start\": 223.0, \"end\": 227.0, \"text\": \"Italian authorities are conducting autopsies on the bodies of\"}, {\"start\": 227.0, \"end\": 235.0, \"text\": \"26 young migrant women possibly from Nigeria and Niger.\"}, {\"start\": 235.0, \"end\": 239.0, \"text\": \"They are believed to be between the ages of 14 and 18.\"}, {\"start\": 240.0, \"end\": 245.0, \"text\": \"Their bodies were found floating near a boat in the central Mediterranean\"}, {\"start\": 245.0, \"end\": 251.0, \"text\": \"off the coast of Libya.\"}, {\"start\": 252.0, \"end\": 256.0, \"text\": \"Many of the women are believed to be from countries that are often associated with\"}, {\"start\": 256.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"sex trafficking rings bringing young girls into\"}, {\"start\": 261.0, \"end\": 265.0, \"text\": \"Italy and forcing them into prostitution.\"}, {\"start\": 265.0, \"end\": 271.0, \"text\": \"Investigators are trying to find out if\"}, {\"start\": 271.0, \"end\": 279.0, \"text\": \"the women were intentionally thrown overboard or whether it was part of an accident.\"}, {\"start\": 283.0, \"end\": 286.0, \"text\": \"A guitar once owned by music superstar Prince\"}, {\"start\": 287.0, \"end\": 291.0, \"text\": \"fetched a whopping seven hundred thousand\"}, {\"start\": 292.0, \"end\": 296.0, \"text\": \"dollars at auction. If you recognize this blue cloud guitar\"}, {\"start\": 297.0, \"end\": 302.0, \"text\": \"it's because the legendary performer used it on\"}, {\"start\": 302.0, \"end\": 307.0, \"text\": \"stage in the late 80s and early 90s.\"}, {\"start\": 307.0, \"end\": 314.0, \"text\": \"He also posed with it for photo shoots and played it in the studio.\"}, {\"start\": 314.0, \"end\": 317.0, \"text\": \"The guitar comes with a letter of authenticity from its maker\"}, {\"start\": 317.0, \"end\": 325.0, \"text\": \"Andy Beech that says he built it for Prince.\"}, {\"start\": 326.0, \"end\": 329.0, \"text\": \"Prince originally donated the guitar to an auction in\"}, {\"start\": 329.0, \"end\": 337.0, \"text\": \"1994 to benefit Los Angeles earthquake relief.\"}, {\"start\": 340.0, \"end\": 343.0, \"text\": \"Today Twitter announced most tweets\"}, {\"start\": 343.0, \"end\": 348.0, \"text\": \"will now fit 280 characters. The limit used to be a 140.\"}, {\"start\": 348.0, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"You should notice the limit increase today.\"}, {\"start\": 354.0, \"end\": 358.0, \"text\": \"The new limit will rollout to Twitter users in almost 40 languages.\"}, {\"start\": 360.0, \"end\": 368.0, \"text\": \"However the new character length won't apply to Japanese, Korean or Chinese tweets.\"}, {\"start\": 368.0, \"end\": 373.0, \"text\": \"That's because those languages can convey twice as much information\"}, {\"start\": 373.0, \"end\": 376.0, \"text\": \"in less space.\"}, {\"start\": 379.0, \"end\": 383.0, \"text\": \"An iPhone glitch is causing typos and frustration.\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 388.0, \"text\": \"Some users say when they type a lower case \\\"i\\\" the phone's auto correct\"}, {\"start\": 388.0, \"end\": 392.0, \"text\": \"feature changes it to an upper case \\\"a\\\" with a symbol.\"}, {\"start\": 393.0, \"end\": 397.0, \"text\": \"The bug appears to be impacting iPhones with the new IOS\"}, {\"start\": 398.0, \"end\": 403.0, \"text\": \"11.1 software. Apple said in an online post on Monday\"}, {\"start\": 403.0, \"end\": 406.0, \"text\": \"that a future update should fix the problem.\"}, {\"start\": 406.0, \"end\": 409.0, \"text\": \"They will also publish a temporary fix\"}, {\"start\": 409.024, \"end\": 413.024, \"text\": \"on Apple.com.\"}, {\"start\": 415.0, \"end\": 419.0, \"text\": \"This dog's owners have found an innovative way to make\"}, {\"start\": 419.0, \"end\": 425.0, \"text\": \"sure their dog can eat. \\\"Tink\\\" is a Labrador Retriever\"}, {\"start\": 425.0, \"end\": 433.0, \"text\": \"and she suffers from megaesophagus -- a condition that makes it hard\"}, {\"start\": 434.0, \"end\": 439.0, \"text\": \"for her to digest her food. So she eats in a doggie\"}, {\"start\": 439.0, \"end\": 444.0, \"text\": \"high chair to keep her upright. Her owners say\"}, {\"start\": 444.0, \"end\": 449.0, \"text\": \"after she eats they burp her like a baby and then they massage her\"}, {\"start\": 449.0, \"end\": 454.0, \"text\": \"throat to help the food go down.\"}, {\"start\": 454.0, \"end\": 459.0, \"text\": \"Other than that Tink's owners say she's a normal dog.\"}, {\"start\": 459.0, \"end\": 467.0, \"text\": \"She loves to go on walks, play Frisbee, cuddle and lick people to death.\"}, {\"start\": 468.1, \"end\": 472.1, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 472.124, \"end\": 477.124, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Remember to like us on Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 477.2, \"end\": 479.2, \"text\": \"and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 479.3, \"end\": 485.3, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "kakTOqKnOzU": {
    "video_id": "kakTOqKnOzU",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.22.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171023",
    "duration": 435,
    "view_count": 290,
    "description": "October 22, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-MANDALAY BAY WON'T RENT OUT SHOOTER'S ROOM\n-OHIO POLICE OFFICER SLAIN\n-'ONE AMERICA' CONCERT\n-FOX GAVE O'REILLY BIG CONTRACT AFTER $32M SETTLEMENT \n-ESPN'S JEMELE HILL RETURNS AFTER 2-WEEK SUSPENSION\n-POLLUTION LINKED TO 9M DEATHS IN 2015\n-WEEKEND BOX OFFICE\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from n",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 11.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.0, \"end\": 21.0, \"text\": \"In Las Vegas MGM Resorts says it has no plans to rent out\"}, {\"start\": 21.0, \"end\": 26.0, \"text\": \"the room on the 32nd floor of the Mandalay Bay Hotel\"}, {\"start\": 26.0, \"end\": 31.0, \"text\": \"where a mass shooting took place. Police say earlier this month\"}, {\"start\": 31.0, \"end\": 36.0, \"text\": \"a man named Stephen Paddock\"}, {\"start\": 36.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"used the room's windows to open fire on an outdoor music\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 46.0, \"text\": \"festival. Fifty eight people died and more than 500 were wounded.\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 51.0, \"text\": \"It's not clear whether the room will be used for something else\"}, {\"start\": 51.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"or marked as a memorial.\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 62.0, \"text\": \"Last night in Ohio a police officer was killed.\"}, {\"start\": 63.0, \"end\": 67.0, \"text\": \"Justin Leo and his partner\"}, {\"start\": 68.0, \"end\": 73.0, \"text\": \"were responding to a call about someone wanting to commit suicide.\"}, {\"start\": 73.0, \"end\": 78.0, \"text\": \"When the officers arrived at the home a man opened the door, chatted with the officers for\"}, {\"start\": 78.0, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"a few minutes, pulled a gun and opened fire.\"}, {\"start\": 81.0, \"end\": 86.0, \"text\": \"Officer Leo was killed instantly. Leo's partner returned fire and killed the shooter.\"}, {\"start\": 86.0, \"end\": 91.0, \"text\": \"Officer Leo was only 31 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 94.0, \"end\": 99.0, \"text\": \"Last night in Texas five former presidents worked together\"}, {\"start\": 99.0, \"end\": 104.0, \"text\": \"to try to help the victims of three recent hurricanes.\"}, {\"start\": 104.0, \"end\": 110.0, \"text\": \"They were Presidents Jimmy Carter,\"}, {\"start\": 111.0, \"end\": 115.0, \"text\": \"George H. W. Bush,\"}, {\"start\": 116.0, \"end\": 119.0, \"text\": \"Bill Clinton,\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 126.0, \"text\": \"George W. Bush and Barack Obama.\"}, {\"start\": 127.0, \"end\": 131.0, \"text\": \"The event took place at Texas A&amp;M University\"}, {\"start\": 131.0, \"end\": 136.0, \"text\": \"which is where George H. W. Bush's presidential\"}, {\"start\": 136.0, \"end\": 140.0, \"text\": \"library is located. The evening was originally planned\"}, {\"start\": 140.0, \"end\": 145.0, \"text\": \"to celebrate the 20th anniversary of the library but\"}, {\"start\": 145.0, \"end\": 151.0, \"text\": \"the presidents decided to turn it into an opportunity to help\"}, {\"start\": 152.0, \"end\": 157.0, \"text\": \"hurricane victims. They named the event One America Appeal charity.\"}, {\"start\": 157.0, \"end\": 163.0, \"text\": \"So far the charity has raised 30 million dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 163.0, \"end\": 168.0, \"text\": \"It's not clear if President Trump was invited but he did\"}, {\"start\": 168.0, \"end\": 173.0, \"text\": \"send a two minute message praising the work of the former presidents.\"}, {\"start\": 174.0, \"end\": 179.0, \"text\": \"And he said he was honored to be given an opportunity to participate\"}, {\"start\": 179.0, \"end\": 181.0, \"text\": \"in relief and recovery efforts.\"}, {\"start\": 182.0, \"end\": 187.0, \"text\": \"Fox News now has another sexual harassment scandal on its hands.\"}, {\"start\": 187.0, \"end\": 194.0, \"text\": \"The New York Times claims that Fox News renewed\"}, {\"start\": 194.0, \"end\": 198.0, \"text\": \"Bill O'Reilly's contract even though it knew\"}, {\"start\": 198.0, \"end\": 203.0, \"text\": \"O'Reilly had paid 32 million dollars to a woman to settle\"}, {\"start\": 203.0, \"end\": 208.0, \"text\": \"a sexual harassment lawsuit. Fox News renewed O'Reilly's\"}, {\"start\": 208.0, \"end\": 213.0, \"text\": \"contract for 25 million dollars a year and\"}, {\"start\": 213.0, \"end\": 218.0, \"text\": \"the new contract included an amendment that would allow Fox News to fire\"}, {\"start\": 218.0, \"end\": 224.0, \"text\": \"O'Reilly if new sexual harassment allegations were leveled against him.\"}, {\"start\": 224.0, \"end\": 228.0, \"text\": \"Just two months later the New York Times discovered other settlements\"}, {\"start\": 229.0, \"end\": 234.0, \"text\": \"with women who had accused O'Reilly of sexual harassment and verbal abuse.\"}, {\"start\": 234.0, \"end\": 238.0, \"text\": \"After the new lawsuits were exposed Fox News fired O'Reilly.\"}, {\"start\": 243.0, \"end\": 248.0, \"text\": \"Tomorrow ESPN host Jemele Hill\"}, {\"start\": 248.0, \"end\": 253.0, \"text\": \"will be back on the air. Her two week suspension\"}, {\"start\": 253.0, \"end\": 258.0, \"text\": \"is complete. Hill was suspended because she violated\"}, {\"start\": 258.0, \"end\": 263.0, \"text\": \"ESPN's social media guidelines twice.\"}, {\"start\": 263.0, \"end\": 268.0, \"text\": \"In one tweet she called President Trump a racist.\"}, {\"start\": 269.0, \"end\": 272.0, \"text\": \"In the second tweet she offended\"}, {\"start\": 274.0, \"end\": 278.0, \"text\": \"Dallas Cowboys owner Jerry Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 278.0, \"end\": 282.0, \"text\": \"Hill admitted she broke the rules.\"}, {\"start\": 282.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"She said she deserved to be suspended and that the network\"}, {\"start\": 287.0, \"end\": 292.0, \"text\": \"did what it thought was right. She also said she's looking forward to\"}, {\"start\": 292.0, \"end\": 297.0, \"text\": \"a good healthy work place with her employer.\"}, {\"start\": 301.0, \"end\": 305.0, \"text\": \"In 2015 an estimated nine million deaths worldwide\"}, {\"start\": 305.0, \"end\": 311.0, \"text\": \"were linked to pollution.\"}, {\"start\": 311.0, \"end\": 316.0, \"text\": \"That's according to a new study by British medical\"}, {\"start\": 317.0, \"end\": 321.0, \"text\": \"journal Lancet. The new study shows that\"}, {\"start\": 321.0, \"end\": 328.0, \"text\": \"air pollution is by far the worst killer followed by water contamination.\"}, {\"start\": 328.0, \"end\": 331.0, \"text\": \"The Journal says that people who are poor and\"}, {\"start\": 331.0, \"end\": 336.0, \"text\": \"marginalized are most likely to fall victim to\"}, {\"start\": 337.0, \"end\": 342.0, \"text\": \"pollution-related diseases.\"}, {\"start\": 344.0, \"end\": 348.0, \"text\": \"This weekend actor Tyler Perry had\"}, {\"start\": 348.0, \"end\": 350.0, \"text\": \"a big day at the movie theaters.\"}, {\"start\": 350.0, \"end\": 355.0, \"text\": \"His comedy Boo Two\"}, {\"start\": 355.0, \"end\": 359.0, \"text\": \"A Madea Halloween\"}, {\"start\": 359.0, \"end\": 364.0, \"text\": \"opened at the top spot.\"}, {\"start\": 364.0, \"end\": 369.0, \"text\": \"The movie raked in close to 22 million dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 373.0, \"text\": \"The sci-fi flick Geostorm\"}, {\"start\": 375.0, \"end\": 379.0, \"text\": \"came in second with 13 million dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 379.0, \"end\": 383.0, \"text\": \"This movie is about a global weather\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 388.0, \"text\": \"disaster. Movie experts believe\"}, {\"start\": 388.0, \"end\": 393.0, \"text\": \"viewers may be turned off by this movie because of the recent hurricanes.\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 397.0, \"text\": \"At number three the horror movie Happy\"}, {\"start\": 397.0, \"end\": 405.0, \"text\": \"Death Day is expected to bring in\"}, {\"start\": 405.024, \"end\": 407.199, \"text\": \"about 9 billion.\"}, {\"start\": 409.0, \"end\": 412.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 412.0, \"end\": 415.0, \"text\": \"I am Jethro Wooddall. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 415.0, \"end\": 420.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 421.0, \"end\": 426.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "ek0Yr1ju7zc": {
    "video_id": "ek0Yr1ju7zc",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.15.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180416",
    "duration": 506,
    "view_count": 2631,
    "description": "4.15.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Arrests spark Starbucks boycott  \n-Syria's Assad meets with Russia after us attacks\n-Trump slams Comey in Sunday tweetstorm\n-Comey hopes people find his book useful \n-Credit card signatures a thing of the past?\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN, FO",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.32, \"end\": 8.7, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.7, \"end\": 11.3, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.3, \"end\": 13.06, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.06, \"end\": 16.86, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.18, \"end\": 24.22, \"text\": \"This video is going viral.\"}, {\"start\": 24.28, \"end\": 34.2, \"text\": \"It shows two black men being handcuffed and taken away at a Philadelphia Starbucks.\"}, {\"start\": 34.2, \"end\": 42.3, \"text\": \"A Starbucks employee called police because the men were just sitting in the restaurant\"}, {\"start\": 42.3, \"end\": 46.54, \"text\": \"and had not ordered anything.\"}, {\"start\": 46.54, \"end\": 54.36, \"text\": \"The men's lawyer says they only waited for less than 15 minutes and did nothing wrong.\"}, {\"start\": 54.36, \"end\": 60.68, \"text\": \"She believes they were singled out because they are black.\"}, {\"start\": 60.68, \"end\": 65.44, \"text\": \"A man in a gray vest later shows up.\"}, {\"start\": 65.44, \"end\": 75.62, \"text\": \"He is a real estate investor and he is heard telling officers the men were waiting to meet\"}, {\"start\": 75.62, \"end\": 88.12, \"text\": \"with him to discuss a deal and repeatedly asked \\\"What did they do?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 88.12, \"end\": 96.5, \"text\": \"Philadelphia's police commissioner is defending the arrest.\"}, {\"start\": 96.5, \"end\": 105.68, \"text\": \"He says a Starbucks employee called police to report a disturbance and accused the men\"}, {\"start\": 105.68, \"end\": 109.1, \"text\": \"of trespassing.\"}, {\"start\": 109.1, \"end\": 121.5, \"text\": \"The men were released from custody at the police station after it became\"}, {\"start\": 121.5, \"end\": 128.72, \"text\": \"that Starbucks did not want to press charges.\"}, {\"start\": 128.72, \"end\": 141.989, \"text\": \"Meanwhile, the video has sparked a major reaction on social media with many calling for a Starbucks\"}, {\"start\": 142.0, \"end\": 145.04, \"text\": \"boycott.\"}, {\"start\": 145.04, \"end\": 155.32, \"text\": \"Starbucks is apologizing to the men and customers, saying they clearly have more work to do when\"}, {\"start\": 155.32, \"end\": 159.88, \"text\": \"it comes to how they handle incidents in their stores.\"}, {\"start\": 159.88, \"end\": 171.36, \"text\": \"Starbucks' CEO says he wants to meet with the two men personally to apologize face-to-face.\"}, {\"start\": 175.76, \"end\": 192.56, \"text\": \"Syrian president Bashar al-Assad met with a group of Russian lawmakers on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 192.56, \"end\": 204.92, \"text\": \"He told the group he believes Friday's military missile strikes on his country were an act\"}, {\"start\": 204.92, \"end\": 208.56, \"text\": \"of aggression.\"}, {\"start\": 208.56, \"end\": 216.8, \"text\": \"Russia accused the US of a major breach of international law and immediately called for\"}, {\"start\": 216.8, \"end\": 221.12, \"text\": \"an emergency meeting of the UN Security Council.\"}, {\"start\": 221.12, \"end\": 236.52, \"text\": \"US Ambassador Nikki Haley responded by saying the time for talk is over and the US is prepared\"}, {\"start\": 236.52, \"end\": 243.64, \"text\": \"to sustain the pressure on Syria if they're foolish enough to test America.\"}, {\"start\": 247.0, \"end\": 258.96, \"text\": \"Apparently Syria wasn't top priority on President Trump's mind this morning, but former FBI\"}, {\"start\": 258.96, \"end\": 265.68, \"text\": \"director James Comey was.\"}, {\"start\": 265.68, \"end\": 273.36, \"text\": \"Trump went on a tweetstorm, slamming Comey in one tweet after another.\"}, {\"start\": 273.36, \"end\": 287.76, \"text\": \"He called Comey slippery, a liar, the worst FBI director in history and a slimeball who\"}, {\"start\": 287.76, \"end\": 290.2, \"text\": \"should be tossed in jail.\"}, {\"start\": 290.2, \"end\": 297.04, \"text\": \"He also called Comey's upcoming book a fake memoir.\"}, {\"start\": 297.04, \"end\": 314.96, \"text\": \"Comey's book \\\"A Higher Loyalty\\\" paints a picture of Trump as a compulsive liar, unethical and\"}, {\"start\": 314.96, \"end\": 320.68, \"text\": \"devoid of human emotions.\"}, {\"start\": 323.8, \"end\": 337.72, \"text\": \"James Comey's only response to Trump's tweetstorm was this one post.\"}, {\"start\": 337.72, \"end\": 353.16, \"text\": \"He said his book is about ethical leadership and he uses stories from his life and lessons\"}, {\"start\": 353.16, \"end\": 356.36, \"text\": \"he's learned from others.\"}, {\"start\": 356.36, \"end\": 370.52, \"text\": \"He says three presidents are mentioned in his book: two of them illustrate the value\"}, {\"start\": 370.52, \"end\": 379.92, \"text\": \"of ethical leadership and one serves as an example of the opposite.\"}, {\"start\": 379.92, \"end\": 387.52, \"text\": \"He hopes people who read the book will find it useful.\"}, {\"start\": 392.08, \"end\": 400.94, \"text\": \"Starting this weekend, several credit card companies scrapped the practice of requiring\"}, {\"start\": 400.94, \"end\": 404.48, \"text\": \"a signature when you swipe your card.\"}, {\"start\": 404.48, \"end\": 413.2, \"text\": \"Starting on Saturday, Visa stopped requiring merchants to collect customer signatures during\"}, {\"start\": 413.2, \"end\": 416.8, \"text\": \"transactions.\"}, {\"start\": 416.8, \"end\": 437.0, \"text\": \"American Express, Discover and MasterCard scrapped the practice Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 437.0, \"end\": 448.24, \"text\": \"One expert says that signatures are not considered a real deterrent to fraud anymore.\"}, {\"start\": 448.24, \"end\": 458.88, \"text\": \"That's partly because most people don't sign their full name anyway.\"}, {\"start\": 458.88, \"end\": 468.84, \"text\": \"But some merchants will still require you to sign because that's built into their credit\"}, {\"start\": 468.84, \"end\": 472.4, \"text\": \"card processing systems.\"}, {\"start\": 475.44, \"end\": 478.56, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 478.56, \"end\": 480.2, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 480.2, \"end\": 483.56, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 483.56, \"end\": 490.04, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 490.04, \"end\": 492.96, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 492.96, \"end\": 495.24, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 495.24, \"end\": 498.16, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "2zj0EooJVG4": {
    "video_id": "2zj0EooJVG4",
    "title": "Photos of damage from Atlanta Airport fire (12.18.17)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171219",
    "duration": 83,
    "view_count": 106,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.96, \"end\": 7.68, \"text\": \"Here's a look at some of the damage from the fire that knocked out power\"}, {\"start\": 7.68, \"end\": 14.4, \"text\": \"to Atlanta's Hartsfield-Jackson International airport.\"}, {\"start\": 14.56, \"end\": 24.48, \"text\": \"Atlanta's mayor said the outage started with a fire in a Georgia Power underground electrical facility.\"}, {\"start\": 24.48, \"end\": 35.52, \"text\": \"He said the electrical fire's intensity damaged two substations serving the airport,\"}, {\"start\": 35.52, \"end\": 53.5, \"text\": \"including the airport's \\\"redundant system\\\" that should have provided backup power.\"}, {\"start\": 53.5, \"end\": 59.92, \"text\": \"The outage lasted nearly 11 hours until late Sunday night.\"}, {\"start\": 59.96, \"end\": 64.06, \"text\": \"It left thousands stranded in dark terminals\"}, {\"start\": 64.06, \"end\": 69.46, \"text\": \"and on planes sitting on the tarmac.\"}, {\"start\": 69.46, \"end\": 74.66, \"text\": \"The ground stop disrupted air travel across the U-S and led to cancellations of more than\"}, {\"start\": 74.66, \"end\": 81.76, \"text\": \"a thousand flights in and out of the airport.\"}]"
  },
  "ks-ZeVsQwbw": {
    "video_id": "ks-ZeVsQwbw",
    "title": "Bridge collapse memorials grow (ASL - 3.16.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180316",
    "duration": 36,
    "view_count": 85,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.84, \"end\": 7.7, \"text\": \"Overnight people started coming to the intersection where the bridge collapsed to light candles\"}, {\"start\": 7.7, \"end\": 13.44, \"text\": \"for those killed and for the ones still trapped under the rubble.\"}, {\"start\": 13.44, \"end\": 21.44, \"text\": \"As you can see many people just sat in silence, some prayed, some cried.\"}, {\"start\": 21.44, \"end\": 27.0, \"text\": \"And this picture was taken from up above.\"}, {\"start\": 27.08, \"end\": 34.92, \"text\": \"Someone placed their candles in the shape of a heart to honor those killed.\"}]"
  },
  "JTEkB9AEaU0": {
    "video_id": "JTEkB9AEaU0",
    "title": "Trump approves release of controversial memo (ASL - 2.2.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180203",
    "duration": 75,
    "view_count": 267,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.64, \"end\": 10.34, \"text\": \"Today President Trump authorized the release of a controversial Republican memo.\"}, {\"start\": 10.34, \"end\": 15.74, \"text\": \"It’s a report from the House Intelligence Committee compiled by Republican Congressman\"}, {\"start\": 15.74, \"end\": 18.22, \"text\": \"Devin Nunes.\"}, {\"start\": 18.22, \"end\": 29.14, \"text\": \"The report accuses the FBI for abusing surveillance powers and accuses the Democrats of being\"}, {\"start\": 29.14, \"end\": 31.6, \"text\": \"behind the Russia investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 31.6, \"end\": 42.22, \"text\": \"The memo was released over objections from the Justice Department and the FBI.\"}, {\"start\": 42.22, \"end\": 49.08, \"text\": \"Both agencies had serious concerns about the document’s accuracy.\"}, {\"start\": 49.08, \"end\": 59.7, \"text\": \"Trump calls the memo a disgrace and sources say he sees it as a way to discredit the entire\"}, {\"start\": 59.7, \"end\": 64.02, \"text\": \"Russia investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 64.02, \"end\": 70.76, \"text\": \"For now, the president refuses to say whether he will fire the top Justice Department official\"}, {\"start\": 70.76, \"end\": 74.1, \"text\": \"overseeing the investigation.\"}]"
  },
  "26P-Ma96pEs": {
    "video_id": "26P-Ma96pEs",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.10.18 - News in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180111",
    "duration": 550,
    "view_count": 821,
    "description": "1.10.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Judge blocks Trump's plan to roll back DACA\n-Deadly mudslides wipe out areas hit by wildfires\n-Lawmakers invited to wear black to support #MeToo\n-State Rep apologizes for racial marijuana comments \n-Widespread flu activity reported in 46 states\n-Amazon CEO Jeff Bezos richest person of all time \n-Hulu grows to 17 million subscribers \n-Focus on fruit\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.88, \"end\": 6.92, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.92, \"end\": 9.06, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.06, \"end\": 10.6, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 10.6, \"end\": 13.02, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.52, \"end\": 24.46, \"text\": \"The Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals (DACA) allows undocumented immigrants brought\"}, {\"start\": 24.46, \"end\": 30.54, \"text\": \"to the US as children to work and go to college.\"}, {\"start\": 30.54, \"end\": 34.0, \"text\": \"Those children have been labeled \\\"dreamers.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 34.0, \"end\": 39.68, \"text\": \"The Trump administration wants to kill the program.\"}, {\"start\": 39.68, \"end\": 46.98, \"text\": \"But a California judge issued a nationwide injunction late Tuesday saying it was improper.\"}, {\"start\": 46.98, \"end\": 57.62, \"text\": \"The judge's ruling means protections for dreamers must remain in place while pending legal challenges\"}, {\"start\": 57.62, \"end\": 61.62, \"text\": \"proceed and it orders the government to resume taking renewal applications for those already\"}, {\"start\": 61.62, \"end\": 62.9, \"text\": \"in the program.\"}, {\"start\": 62.9, \"end\": 69.6, \"text\": \"But the judge who issued the ruling says the Trump administration does not have to accept\"}, {\"start\": 69.68, \"end\": 71.6, \"text\": \"first-time applications.\"}, {\"start\": 77.2, \"end\": 83.4, \"text\": \"Residents in several Southern California towns were abruptly woken up in the early morning\"}, {\"start\": 83.44, \"end\": 89.2, \"text\": \"hours to rivers of mud and debris flowing through their neighborhoods.\"}, {\"start\": 89.2, \"end\": 98.6, \"text\": \"Unfortunately people there are still trying to recover from last month's massive wildfires.\"}, {\"start\": 98.64, \"end\": 104.96, \"text\": \"But because all the vegetation was destroyed by fire, there was nothing left to hold the\"}, {\"start\": 104.96, \"end\": 107.12, \"text\": \"hillsides together when the rains came.\"}, {\"start\": 107.12, \"end\": 109.72, \"text\": \"As a result everything came crashing down in a muddy mess.\"}, {\"start\": 109.72, \"end\": 113.08, \"text\": \"Homes are being wiped off their foundations.\"}, {\"start\": 113.16, \"end\": 119.2, \"text\": \"Roads are impassable and part of the 101 freeway had to be shut down when the flooding and\"}, {\"start\": 119.28, \"end\": 120.92, \"text\": \"mud made its way downhill.\"}, {\"start\": 120.92, \"end\": 125.0, \"text\": \"15 people have been killed and at least 50 people had to be rescued from their homes\"}, {\"start\": 125.0, \"end\": 128.28, \"text\": \"by helicopter.\"}, {\"start\": 131.16, \"end\": 137.88, \"text\": \"Some members of Congress plan to wear all black during President Trump's first State\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 142.68, \"text\": \"of the Union address later this month.\"}, {\"start\": 142.68, \"end\": 152.48, \"text\": \"The gesture is meant to show support for the anti-sexual harassment #METOO and #TIMESUP\"}, {\"start\": 152.48, \"end\": 155.56, \"text\": \"movements.\"}, {\"start\": 155.64, \"end\": 163.32, \"text\": \"The sexual harassment scandal has plagued Congress in recent weeks, forcing some Congress\"}, {\"start\": 163.32, \"end\": 165.68, \"text\": \"members to resign from office.\"}, {\"start\": 165.68, \"end\": 174.64, \"text\": \"Organizers of this event are encouraging men and women, Republicans and Democrats to dress\"}, {\"start\": 174.64, \"end\": 176.4, \"text\": \"in black.\"}, {\"start\": 176.4, \"end\": 180.08, \"text\": \"The State of the Union address is January 30th.\"}, {\"start\": 182.48, \"end\": 193.32, \"text\": \"Kansas State Representative Steve Alford is being widely condemned for his controversial\"}, {\"start\": 193.32, \"end\": 199.08, \"text\": \"public comments about drug use among African-Americans.\"}, {\"start\": 199.08, \"end\": 206.12, \"text\": \"The 75-year-old Republican was speaking to an all-white group at a hospital over the\"}, {\"start\": 206.12, \"end\": 208.32, \"text\": \"weekend to argue against legalizing marijuana in Kansas.\"}, {\"start\": 208.32, \"end\": 216.32, \"text\": \"He said African-Americans use more drugs due to their character makeup and genetics.\"}, {\"start\": 216.48, \"end\": 221.64, \"text\": \"The racially-charged remarks were caught on tape.\"}, {\"start\": 221.64, \"end\": 227.24, \"text\": \"After facing public outcry and mounting condemnation from state officials, Alford issued an apology\"}, {\"start\": 227.24, \"end\": 230.72, \"text\": \"saying he was wrong and regrets what he said.\"}, {\"start\": 230.72, \"end\": 236.56, \"text\": \"Then on Tuesday, he resigned from two House leadership positions.\"}, {\"start\": 236.68, \"end\": 243.32, \"text\": \"It's not clear if those two resignations are linked to his racist remarks.\"}, {\"start\": 245.84, \"end\": 251.24, \"text\": \"Have you been coughing and sniffling over the past few days?\"}, {\"start\": 251.36, \"end\": 255.32, \"text\": \"The flu bug has reared its ugly head once again and is creeping across much of the country.\"}, {\"start\": 255.32, \"end\": 261.84, \"text\": \"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) reports widespread flu activity in 46\"}, {\"start\": 261.84, \"end\": 263.52, \"text\": \"states.\"}, {\"start\": 263.52, \"end\": 269.56, \"text\": \"The bug is especially bad in California with 27 deaths linked to the flu.\"}, {\"start\": 269.56, \"end\": 275.84, \"text\": \"Officials say this flu could be as severe as a 2014-2015 season, which was the most\"}, {\"start\": 275.84, \"end\": 277.52, \"text\": \"severe in years.\"}, {\"start\": 277.52, \"end\": 286.52, \"text\": \"The H-3-N-2 virus is the main strain making people sick and it's tough to fight.\"}, {\"start\": 286.52, \"end\": 291.6, \"text\": \"To make matters worse, some drugstores are dealing with temporary shortages of flu medication\"}, {\"start\": 291.84, \"end\": 294.8, \"text\": \"due to demand.\"}, {\"start\": 294.8, \"end\": 304.04, \"text\": \"The CDC says you can help limit the spread of the flu by wash your hands often and disinfecting\"}, {\"start\": 304.12, \"end\": 307.36, \"text\": \"spots that are touched frequently.\"}, {\"start\": 307.36, \"end\": 312.84, \"text\": \"And of course officials say it's never too late to get a flu shot.\"}, {\"start\": 315.08, \"end\": 325.04, \"text\": \"Amazon CEO Jeff Bezos is now the richest person in history, dethroning former recordholder\"}, {\"start\": 325.04, \"end\": 329.0, \"text\": \"Bill Gates.\"}, {\"start\": 329.0, \"end\": 337.56, \"text\": \"According to Bloomberg's Billionaire tracker, Bezos' net worth has reached just over $105\"}, {\"start\": 337.68, \"end\": 340.56, \"text\": \"billion.\"}, {\"start\": 340.56, \"end\": 345.56, \"text\": \"Most of Bezos' wealth comes from his Amazon holdings.\"}, {\"start\": 345.56, \"end\": 354.56, \"text\": \"He made roughly $1.4 billion in gains Monday when Amazon stock climbed nearly one and a\"}, {\"start\": 354.56, \"end\": 358.12, \"text\": \"half percent.\"}, {\"start\": 361.08, \"end\": 367.04, \"text\": \"Hulu's number of subscribers is skyrocketing!\"}, {\"start\": 367.04, \"end\": 373.5, \"text\": \"The streaming service announced Tuesday it has grown to more than 17 million subscribers.\"}, {\"start\": 373.5, \"end\": 377.5, \"text\": \"That's a 40-percent increase in less than two years.\"}, {\"start\": 377.5, \"end\": 390.4, \"text\": \"Golden Globe winning drama \\\"The Handmaid's Tale\\\" may have played a part in its success.\"}, {\"start\": 390.4, \"end\": 399.16, \"text\": \"The series won 2 awards Sunday night and it was among the most-watched dramas on Hulu\"}, {\"start\": 399.16, \"end\": 404.72, \"text\": \"2017.\"}, {\"start\": 408.28, \"end\": 415.36, \"text\": \"Improving your health is a top New Year's resolution and little changes to your diet\"}, {\"start\": 415.36, \"end\": 418.48, \"text\": \"can make a big difference.\"}, {\"start\": 418.48, \"end\": 432.72, \"text\": \"Most fruits are naturally low in calories, sodium and fat and contain essential nutrients.\"}, {\"start\": 432.72, \"end\": 437.36, \"text\": \"Here are some quick tips for working more fruit into your daily routine.\"}, {\"start\": 437.36, \"end\": 444.6, \"text\": \"Try to eat mostly whole or cut up fruit so you can get the beneficial fiber it contains.\"}, {\"start\": 444.84, \"end\": 452.56, \"text\": \"Buy fruit in season when its most flavorful and least expensive.\"}, {\"start\": 452.56, \"end\": 455.4, \"text\": \"Make sure you rinse fruit well before eating or preparing it.\"}, {\"start\": 455.4, \"end\": 459.88, \"text\": \"Scrub briskly under clean running water to remove dirt and any organisms on the surface.\"}, {\"start\": 459.88, \"end\": 464.52, \"text\": \"Set up visible reminders of fruit.\"}, {\"start\": 464.56, \"end\": 472.36, \"text\": \"Keep a bowl filled with your favorites on a counter, table or in the refrigerator.\"}, {\"start\": 472.52, \"end\": 476.64, \"text\": \"Work in some variety.\"}, {\"start\": 476.64, \"end\": 479.36, \"text\": \"Have dried, frozen and canned options on hand so you never have to go without your fruit\"}, {\"start\": 479.36, \"end\": 481.16, \"text\": \"fix.\"}, {\"start\": 481.16, \"end\": 491.64, \"text\": \"Fruit makes a great travel snack but it can be a part of any meal.\"}, {\"start\": 491.72, \"end\": 505.04, \"text\": \"Blueberries, bananas, peaches and strawberries are all great with pancakes, in yogurt or\"}, {\"start\": 505.04, \"end\": 506.48, \"text\": \"in cereal.\"}, {\"start\": 506.48, \"end\": 512.24, \"text\": \"Fruit can be added to salads at lunch or dinner.\"}, {\"start\": 512.24, \"end\": 515.0, \"text\": \"Or you can have it as a dessert after a meal.\"}, {\"start\": 515.0, \"end\": 518.6, \"text\": \"And if you have kids, be a good role model.\"}, {\"start\": 518.6, \"end\": 525.88, \"text\": \"Let them see you eating nutritious fruit everyday.\"}, {\"start\": 528.64, \"end\": 531.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 531.0, \"end\": 532.28, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 532.28, \"end\": 534.52, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 534.52, \"end\": 538.64, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 538.64, \"end\": 544.48, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "egM34eDINwg": {
    "video_id": "egM34eDINwg",
    "title": "“Bomb cyclone” kills six, 900K without power (ASL - 3.4.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180305",
    "duration": 78,
    "view_count": 95,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.86, \"end\": 14.62, \"text\": \"The \\\"bomb cyclone\\\" that hammered the Northeast this weekend has now moved out to sea but\"}, {\"start\": 14.62, \"end\": 17.04, \"text\": \"it left a lot of devastation behind.\"}, {\"start\": 17.04, \"end\": 24.7, \"text\": \"The storm killed at least six people and more than 600,000 people from Virginia to Massachusetts\"}, {\"start\": 24.7, \"end\": 26.93, \"text\": \"are without power.\"}, {\"start\": 26.93, \"end\": 34.78, \"text\": \"At one point, homes and buildings in the Boston area were completely underwater.\"}, {\"start\": 34.78, \"end\": 43.34, \"text\": \"In the nearby town of Quincy, police say they performed more than 250 rescues Friday and\"}, {\"start\": 43.34, \"end\": 45.15, \"text\": \"Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 45.15, \"end\": 52.38, \"text\": \"The storm also dumped heavy snow from Ohio to New England and into upstate New York,\"}, {\"start\": 52.38, \"end\": 55.04, \"text\": \"where more than 3 feet of snow was recorded.\"}, {\"start\": 55.04, \"end\": 60.719, \"text\": \"Massachusetts, Virginia and Maryland have issued emergency declaration.\"}, {\"start\": 60.72, \"end\": 66.3, \"text\": \"That allows state and local agencies to help those affected by the storm.\"}, {\"start\": 66.3, \"end\": 75.7, \"text\": \"Nearly 15 million people remained under a coastal flooding warning Saturday afternoon.\"}]"
  },
  "-jar_eJa87Y": {
    "video_id": "-jar_eJa87Y",
    "title": "Equifax hackers stole more than previously reported (ASL - 3.1.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180302",
    "duration": 43,
    "view_count": 54,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.9, \"end\": 10.86, \"text\": \"Last year Equifax announced that hackers stole the personal information of 145.5 million people.\"}, {\"start\": 10.86, \"end\": 17.2, \"text\": \"That included Social Security numbers, driver's license numbers and addresses.\"}, {\"start\": 17.2, \"end\": 23.36, \"text\": \"Now Equifax says it has discovered another 2.4 million Americans who had their names\"}, {\"start\": 23.36, \"end\": 29.4, \"text\": \"and driver's license numbers exposed.\"}, {\"start\": 29.4, \"end\": 37.74, \"text\": \"The company said it will notify the newly discovered victims and offer free identity\"}, {\"start\": 37.74, \"end\": 42.1, \"text\": \"theft protection and credit monitoring.\"}]"
  },
  "TO2FhCTc-UM": {
    "video_id": "TO2FhCTc-UM",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.4.2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171205",
    "duration": 627,
    "view_count": 678,
    "description": "December 4, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-18-YEAR OLD SAYS HE MOLESTED 50+ CHILDREN\n-SMU POLICE WANT HELP IN HATE BANNERS CASE\n-TRUMP ROLLS BACK UTAH MONUMENT DESIGNATIONS\n-OBESE KIDS FORECAST\n-FACEBOOK MESSENGER KIDS APP\n-INCREDIBLE IMAGES OF THE SUPERMOON\n-TEXTING TURNS 25!\n-ASTRONAUTS HAVE PIZZA PARTY IN ZERO GRAVITY\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We ha",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.06, \"end\": 8.8, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.8, \"end\": 10.8, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.8, \"end\": 12.16, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 12.16, \"end\": 14.96, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.0, \"end\": 24.9, \"text\": \"Police in Southern California arrested 18-year-old Joseph Boston for\"}, {\"start\": 24.9, \"end\": 29.78, \"text\": \"molesting children after his mother turned him in.\"}, {\"start\": 29.8, \"end\": 36.86, \"text\": \"Boston called his mother and told her that he sexually molested two children\"}, {\"start\": 36.86, \"end\": 44.7, \"text\": \"at the Extended Stay hotel where he lives.\"}, {\"start\": 44.72, \"end\": 53.46, \"text\": \"She picked him up and took him to the police station at 3 AM Saturday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 53.5, \"end\": 58.4, \"text\": \"He confessed to molesting an eight-year-old and four-year-old boy who were staying at\"}, {\"start\": 58.44, \"end\": 62.04, \"text\": \"the same hotel with their parents.\"}, {\"start\": 62.1, \"end\": 68.62, \"text\": \"Boston also told police he had been abusing children since he was 10 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 68.68, \"end\": 74.56, \"text\": \"He says he has molested 50 or more kids in multiple cities.\"}, {\"start\": 74.58, \"end\": 79.7, \"text\": \"A judge set his bail at $1 million.\"}, {\"start\": 80.88, \"end\": 89.22, \"text\": \"Southern Methodist University police are asking for help identifying suspects who may have\"}, {\"start\": 89.26, \"end\": 95.52, \"text\": \"helped post racist fliers on campus.\"}, {\"start\": 95.52, \"end\": 107.5, \"text\": \"Police released these images showing the suspects carrying a banner.\"}, {\"start\": 107.5, \"end\": 116.02, \"text\": \"The signs posted at the school said things like \\\"No more tolerance\\\", \\\"No more diversity\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 116.04, \"end\": 120.38, \"text\": \"and \\\"Protect white lives.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 120.38, \"end\": 131.02, \"text\": \"A group called \\\"Texas Vanguard\\\" claimed responsibility on Twitter for the fliers and banner.\"}, {\"start\": 131.02, \"end\": 139.24, \"text\": \"SMU's president says anyone involved with this group and is affiliated with the school\"}, {\"start\": 139.26, \"end\": 141.5, \"text\": \"will face disciplinary action.\"}, {\"start\": 143.02, \"end\": 155.1, \"text\": \"On Monday President Trump announced that he will downsize two national monuments in Utah.\"}, {\"start\": 155.16, \"end\": 167.54, \"text\": \"Trump will shrink Bears End national monument by more than 80%\"}, {\"start\": 167.58, \"end\": 182.78, \"text\": \"and the Grand Staircase Escalante national monument by roughly 45%.\"}, {\"start\": 182.8, \"end\": 189.2, \"text\": \"Trump slammed past administrations' protection designations\"}, {\"start\": 189.22, \"end\": 194.48, \"text\": \"for large swaths of land as \\\"federal overreach.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 194.5, \"end\": 202.48, \"text\": \"Monday's announcement makes Trump the first modern president to significantly shrink a\"}, {\"start\": 202.48, \"end\": 224.86, \"text\": \"national monument using the 1906 Antiquities Act.\"}, {\"start\": 224.86, \"end\": 235.52, \"text\": \"Interior Secretary Ryan Zinke says no federal land will be transferred or sold but Trump's\"}, {\"start\": 235.52, \"end\": 244.78, \"text\": \"downsizing of the two monuments will most likely be challenged in court.\"}, {\"start\": 245.82, \"end\": 253.46, \"text\": \"New computer analysis predicts a majority of the kids growing up in the US\"}, {\"start\": 253.48, \"end\": 257.94, \"text\": \"will be obese by the time they turned 35 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 257.94, \"end\": 269.64, \"text\": \"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention says roughly 20% of American children\"}, {\"start\": 269.64, \"end\": 274.42, \"text\": \"6 to 19 years old are already obese.\"}, {\"start\": 274.48, \"end\": 279.88, \"text\": \"But there are ways parents can reverse the trend.\"}, {\"start\": 279.88, \"end\": 293.26, \"text\": \"Make food interesting for kids so they are not always craving processed and fast foods.\"}, {\"start\": 293.26, \"end\": 300.9, \"text\": \"Teach them to read food labels.\"}, {\"start\": 300.9, \"end\": 306.68, \"text\": \"Get them involved by showing them how to cook and make different meals.\"}, {\"start\": 306.76, \"end\": 316.96, \"text\": \"Take them to the local farmers market so they can see how and where various foods are grown.\"}, {\"start\": 316.96, \"end\": 319.48, \"text\": \"Also give them choices.\"}, {\"start\": 319.48, \"end\": 321.84, \"text\": \"Let them choose a healthy snack.\"}, {\"start\": 321.88, \"end\": 327.12, \"text\": \"And parents you can be a huge influence.\"}, {\"start\": 327.2, \"end\": 334.28, \"text\": \"If you eat healthy and stay active, chances are your kids will too.\"}, {\"start\": 335.44, \"end\": 342.12, \"text\": \"Facebook wants to add kids under 13 to its 2 billion users.\"}, {\"start\": 342.139, \"end\": 349.34, \"text\": \"The social network announced a new stand-alone app geared to \\\"Messenger Kids.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 349.34, \"end\": 361.84, \"text\": \"Preteens can use the app to chat with their friends, make calls with kid-friendly filters\"}, {\"start\": 361.84, \"end\": 366.6, \"text\": \"and send age-appropriate images.\"}, {\"start\": 366.6, \"end\": 380.92, \"text\": \"Parents must set up accounts for their children and approve who they can communicate with.\"}, {\"start\": 380.96, \"end\": 390.28, \"text\": \"Facebook promises it will collect little data about Messenger Kids users\"}, {\"start\": 390.36, \"end\": 395.92, \"text\": \"and will not allow them to make purchases.\"}, {\"start\": 395.92, \"end\": 404.84, \"text\": \"The rules for traditional Facebook services are not changing.\"}, {\"start\": 404.84, \"end\": 409.92, \"text\": \"Kids still have to be 13 years old to get their own accounts.\"}, {\"start\": 409.92, \"end\": 423.76, \"text\": \"A preview version of Messenger Kids rolls out today on Apple devices.\"}, {\"start\": 423.76, \"end\": 432.88, \"text\": \"Android and Kindle versions are coming later.\"}, {\"start\": 434.12, \"end\": 442.2, \"text\": \"Sunday night stargazers, astronomers and curious sky watchers got a chance to witness\"}, {\"start\": 442.2, \"end\": 446.44, \"text\": \"the first and only Supermoon of this year.\"}, {\"start\": 446.44, \"end\": 457.23, \"text\": \"Supermoons happen when the sun and Earth align, and a full or new moon aligns with\"}, {\"start\": 457.23, \"end\": 460.66, \"text\": \"the sun's lunar orb.\"}, {\"start\": 460.66, \"end\": 467.08, \"text\": \"Supermoons tend to be brighter and appear to be larger than its usual size.\"}, {\"start\": 467.16, \"end\": 473.56, \"text\": \"The last Supernoon happened in November 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 473.6, \"end\": 478.16, \"text\": \"Two more will be visible in January.\"}, {\"start\": 478.16, \"end\": 489.92, \"text\": \"Astronomers say the best time to catch a glimpse of a Supermoon is either right after sunset\"}, {\"start\": 489.96, \"end\": 493.8, \"text\": \"or minutes before the next sunrise.\"}, {\"start\": 495.32, \"end\": 505.12, \"text\": \"In case you missed it we marked an important milestone over the weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 505.2, \"end\": 508.96, \"text\": \"Texting is now 25 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 509.04, \"end\": 512.04, \"text\": \"The first ever text message was sent on\"}, {\"start\": 512.04, \"end\": 515.76, \"text\": \"December 3, 1992.\"}, {\"start\": 515.76, \"end\": 524.72, \"text\": \"Back then they were called short message service or SMS.\"}, {\"start\": 524.8, \"end\": 536.52, \"text\": \"British engineer Neil Papworth sent the first ever text message from his computer\"}, {\"start\": 536.56, \"end\": 541.12, \"text\": \"to a cell phone.\"}, {\"start\": 541.12, \"end\": 546.28, \"text\": \"It was a two word message: Merry Christmas.\"}, {\"start\": 546.32, \"end\": 556.08, \"text\": \"Papworth says the person he sent the message to wasn't able to reply because\"}, {\"start\": 556.08, \"end\": 565.4, \"text\": \"people could only receive text messages back then.\"}, {\"start\": 566.96, \"end\": 575.2, \"text\": \"Astronauts on the International Space Station got to enjoy a quick pizza fix in zero gravity.\"}, {\"start\": 575.2, \"end\": 585.28, \"text\": \"During a live stream event one astronaut mentioned to his boss how much he missed pizza.\"}, {\"start\": 585.36, \"end\": 591.12, \"text\": \"So all the necessary ingredients were set up to the space station.\"}, {\"start\": 591.16, \"end\": 603.44, \"text\": \"The astronauts sent back this amazing video of the crew making pizzas for movie night.\"}, {\"start\": 605.0, \"end\": 606.4, \"text\": \"Those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 606.4, \"end\": 607.62, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 607.62, \"end\": 610.24, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 610.24, \"end\": 614.4, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 614.56, \"end\": 618.96, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "lurseCKY1dg": {
    "video_id": "lurseCKY1dg",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.4.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180205",
    "duration": 364,
    "view_count": 1078,
    "description": "2.4.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Dramatic video: officer shoots, kills suspect (2.4.18)\n-South Carolina train crash (2.4.18)\n-Hawaii worker who sent missile alert speaks out (2.4.18)\n-Ballet dancers protest by performing in the street (2.4.18)\n-Happy Birthday Candace! (2.4.18)\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Langu",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.88, \"end\": 8.84, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.84, \"end\": 11.08, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.08, \"end\": 12.24, \"text\": \"I’m Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.24, \"end\": 15.52, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.04, \"end\": 23.32, \"text\": \"A Georgia police officer shoots a man who reportedly tried to stab him.\"}, {\"start\": 23.32, \"end\": 29.16, \"text\": \"Clayton County police say the suspect crashed his vehicle after the officer tried to pull\"}, {\"start\": 29.2, \"end\": 31.72, \"text\": \"them over for speeding.\"}, {\"start\": 31.72, \"end\": 38.12, \"text\": \"Dashcam footage shows the officer approaching the suspect’s car.\"}, {\"start\": 38.2, \"end\": 42.48, \"text\": \"The officer could be heard repeatedly yelling “Stay right there! Don't you move! Do not move!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 42.48, \"end\": 51.36, \"text\": \"But the suspect gets on top of his car and lunges through the air at the officer.\"}, {\"start\": 51.56, \"end\": 59.04, \"text\": \"The officer yells that he will shoot him, but the suspect keeps attacking.\"}, {\"start\": 59.04, \"end\": 63.56, \"text\": \"Three shots then ring out and the suspect collapses to the ground.\"}, {\"start\": 63.56, \"end\": 70.44, \"text\": \"We have the video of the entire encounter but due to its graphic nature, we freeze the\"}, {\"start\": 70.72, \"end\": 73.92, \"text\": \"video just as the officer shoots.\"}, {\"start\": 73.92, \"end\": 75.12, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 90.08, \"end\": 95.28, \"text\": \"The officer, along with other deputies, gave first aid to the suspect until an ambulance\"}, {\"start\": 95.28, \"end\": 96.8, \"text\": \"arrives.\"}, {\"start\": 96.8, \"end\": 99.2, \"text\": \"But he died at the scene.\"}, {\"start\": 99.2, \"end\": 103.6, \"text\": \"The officer who fired the shots has been placed on administrative leave until the investigation\"}, {\"start\": 104.0, \"end\": 108.8, \"text\": \"is complete.\"}, {\"start\": 110.48, \"end\": 116.32, \"text\": \"Authorities say two people were killed in a crash involving an Amtrak passenger train\"}, {\"start\": 116.32, \"end\": 127.68, \"text\": \"and a CSX freight train early Sunday in South Carolina.\"}, {\"start\": 127.68, \"end\": 135.04, \"text\": \"One hundred sixteen people were injured, with injuries ranging from scratches to broken\"}, {\"start\": 135.04, \"end\": 137.84, \"text\": \"bones.\"}, {\"start\": 137.84, \"end\": 140.56, \"text\": \"The crash happened about 2:30 Sunday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 140.56, \"end\": 150.64, \"text\": \"The Amtrak train was traveling between New York and Miami with 147 people on board when\"}, {\"start\": 150.64, \"end\": 154.08, \"text\": \"it collided with the freight train, which was sitting on the track.\"}, {\"start\": 154.08, \"end\": 160.88, \"text\": \"The Amtrak train engineer and conductor were killed.\"}, {\"start\": 160.88, \"end\": 168.08, \"text\": \"About 5,000 gallons of fuel spilled but authorities say the spill was not a threat to the public.\"}, {\"start\": 168.08, \"end\": 177.76, \"text\": \"The National Transportation Safety Board says it will take 12 to 18 months to complete its\"}, {\"start\": 177.76, \"end\": 180.4, \"text\": \"investigation into what caused the crash.\"}, {\"start\": 182.56, \"end\": 190.79, \"text\": \"For the first time, we’re hearing from the former state worker who caused panic and chaos\"}, {\"start\": 190.8, \"end\": 201.36, \"text\": \"after sending out a false missile alert for Hawaii.\"}, {\"start\": 201.36, \"end\": 209.36, \"text\": \"The worker doesn’t want to be identified so he’s only known as “Employee One.”\"}, {\"start\": 209.36, \"end\": 218.0, \"text\": \"He says he was 100 percent positive the missile attack was real because he never heard the\"}, {\"start\": 218.08, \"end\": 222.64, \"text\": \"word “exercise” to indicate it was just a drill.\"}, {\"start\": 222.64, \"end\": 228.32, \"text\": \"He says he did what he was trained to do.\"}, {\"start\": 228.32, \"end\": 235.6, \"text\": \"He goes on to say the failure was a statewide system failure because the unplanned drill\"}, {\"start\": 235.6, \"end\": 239.92, \"text\": \"took place as workers were changing shifts and people were not ready.\"}, {\"start\": 239.92, \"end\": 245.52, \"text\": \"The official investigation report contradicts the former state employee.\"}, {\"start\": 245.52, \"end\": 251.6, \"text\": \"It states five other workers did hear the word “exercise” that day.\"}, {\"start\": 251.6, \"end\": 256.72, \"text\": \"“Employee One” has been fired but he says he plans to file an appeal to get his job\"}, {\"start\": 256.72, \"end\": 258.76, \"text\": \"back.\"}, {\"start\": 258.82, \"end\": 264.46, \"text\": \"He’s also considering suing the state for defamation.\"}, {\"start\": 266.88, \"end\": 279.62, \"text\": \"Eighty Argentinian ballet dancers and choreographers lost their jobs in December because of government\"}, {\"start\": 279.62, \"end\": 282.18, \"text\": \"funding cuts.\"}, {\"start\": 282.18, \"end\": 287.08, \"text\": \"They decided to protest this weekend by dancing in the street.\"}, {\"start\": 287.08, \"end\": 291.44, \"text\": \"They stretched and warmed up at the barre.\"}, {\"start\": 291.44, \"end\": 297.44, \"text\": \"Then they started dancing to “Swan Lake.”\"}, {\"start\": 297.44, \"end\": 301.86, \"text\": \"The protest blocked traffic for hours.\"}, {\"start\": 301.98, \"end\": 310.66, \"text\": \"Some drivers leaned into their horns out of frustration while others started cheering\"}, {\"start\": 310.66, \"end\": 313.52, \"text\": \"and applauding.\"}, {\"start\": 314.96, \"end\": 323.24, \"text\": \"Today is Sign1News anchor Candace Jones’ birthday.\"}, {\"start\": 323.24, \"end\": 328.2, \"text\": \"If you’re following her on social media, please take a moment to wish her a very happy\"}, {\"start\": 328.2, \"end\": 330.12, \"text\": \"birthday.\"}, {\"start\": 330.12, \"end\": 335.92, \"text\": \"From all of us here is Sign1News – HAPPY BIRTHDAY CANDACE!\"}, {\"start\": 337.18, \"end\": 339.64, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 339.68, \"end\": 341.06, \"text\": \"I’m Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 341.06, \"end\": 343.8, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 343.8, \"end\": 348.88, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 348.94, \"end\": 356.06, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "i8KzxRhzQks": {
    "video_id": "i8KzxRhzQks",
    "title": "Health benefits of chocolate (ASL - 2.13.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180214",
    "duration": 47,
    "view_count": 356,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.54, \"end\": 11.28, \"text\": \"Tomorrow is Valentine's Day and if you don't know what to get your significant other, try\"}, {\"start\": 11.28, \"end\": 13.36, \"text\": \"chocolate.\"}, {\"start\": 13.36, \"end\": 17.76, \"text\": \"It's not only a romantic gift but it also has several health benefits.\"}, {\"start\": 17.76, \"end\": 26.12, \"text\": \"Researchers say a quarter of an ounce of dark chocolate everyday lowers your risk of a heart\"}, {\"start\": 26.12, \"end\": 38.6, \"text\": \"attack or stroke, it helps reduce inflammation in the body and it definitely improves a person's\"}, {\"start\": 38.6, \"end\": 41.1, \"text\": \"mood.\"}, {\"start\": 41.1, \"end\": 46.1, \"text\": \"But remember moderation is the key.\"}]"
  },
  "R0QXjeGVQEc": {
    "video_id": "R0QXjeGVQEc",
    "title": "Father of FL shooting victim paints powerful mural (ASL - 3.12.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180313",
    "duration": 58,
    "view_count": 86,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.02, \"end\": 8.78, \"text\": \"Manuel Oliver painted this mural to honor his late son.\"}, {\"start\": 8.98, \"end\": 18.68, \"text\": \"Joaquin Oliver was among the 17 students and teachers killed in the February 14 shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 18.68, \"end\": 32.16, \"text\": \"The mural reads \\\"We Demand A Change.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 32.16, \"end\": 39.16, \"text\": \"The artwork is part of the \\\"Parkland 17\\\" exhibit, an art exhibit organized by Miami Heat player\"}, {\"start\": 39.16, \"end\": 57.34, \"text\": \"Dwayne Wade and created by Miami-area artists Evan Pestain.\"}]"
  },
  "eDM9jW83VRo": {
    "video_id": "eDM9jW83VRo",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.21.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171222",
    "duration": 419,
    "view_count": 452,
    "description": "December 21, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-UN VOTES TO CONDEMN TRUMP'S JERUSALEM DECISION\n-RYAN AND HATCH SIGN GOP TAX BILL\n-N. KOREA \"GHOST SHIPS\" WASHING UP IN JAPAN\n-APPLE ADMITS IT'S SLOWING DOWN OLDER IPHONES\n-PRINCE HARRY, MEGHAN MARKLE ENGAGEMENT PHOTOS\n-WINTER BEGINS TODAY!\n-GIRL SAVES DAVE & BUSTER TICKETS, BUYS GIFTS FOR NEEDY KIDS\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leade",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.78, \"end\": 8.82, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.82, \"end\": 11.12, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.14, \"end\": 12.5, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.5, \"end\": 14.98, \"text\": \"Here are top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.24, \"end\": 29.14, \"text\": \"Today the United Nations voted overwhelmingly to condemn President Trump's decision to recognize\"}, {\"start\": 29.14, \"end\": 32.14, \"text\": \"Jerusalem as the capital of Israel.\"}, {\"start\": 32.14, \"end\": 41.74, \"text\": \"128 countries voted in support of the resolution, nine voted \\\"no\\\" and 35 nations abstained,\"}, {\"start\": 41.8, \"end\": 46.6, \"text\": \"including Canada, Mexico and Australia.\"}, {\"start\": 46.68, \"end\": 56.76, \"text\": \"The vote came right after US Ambassador Nikki Haley issued a direct threat, saying that\"}, {\"start\": 56.76, \"end\": 62.92, \"text\": \"the US will pull funding from the UN if it voted to condemn Trump's decision.\"}, {\"start\": 62.92, \"end\": 69.52, \"text\": \"Apparently the threat didn't work because country after country blasted the US.\"}, {\"start\": 69.6, \"end\": 75.88, \"text\": \"Her comments were followed by a threat from Trump himself who said \\\"Let them vote against us.\"}, {\"start\": 75.88, \"end\": 80.64, \"text\": \"We'll save a lot of money. We don't care.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 80.64, \"end\": 91.72, \"text\": \"The UN said Trump decision was illegal, it will cause instability in the Middle East and it\"}, {\"start\": 91.8, \"end\": 95.16, \"text\": \"is a violation of international law.\"}, {\"start\": 97.32, \"end\": 110.08, \"text\": \"House and Senate leaders Paul Ryan and Orrin Hatch signed the new tax bill on Thursday.\"}, {\"start\": 110.28, \"end\": 115.96, \"text\": \"Both lawmakers played a key role in making the bill.\"}, {\"start\": 116.12, \"end\": 127.56, \"text\": \"Republicans say the bill will help middle-class families and lead to more jobs.\"}, {\"start\": 127.56, \"end\": 134.48, \"text\": \"The White House has not yet announced an official time President Trump will sign the bill.\"}, {\"start\": 136.52, \"end\": 145.48, \"text\": \"A growing and disturbing trend is taking place off the coast of Japan.\"}, {\"start\": 145.6, \"end\": 153.68, \"text\": \"The Japanese Coast Guard says a record number of close to 100 North Korean fishing boats\"}, {\"start\": 153.76, \"end\": 157.4, \"text\": \"have washed up on its beaches recently.\"}, {\"start\": 157.4, \"end\": 161.76, \"text\": \"In those boats are the bodies of North Korean fishermen.\"}, {\"start\": 162.16, \"end\": 166.629, \"text\": \"They've named the boats \\\"ghosts ships.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 166.64, \"end\": 174.4, \"text\": \"Japan is more than 600 miles from North Korea.\"}, {\"start\": 174.4, \"end\": 180.2, \"text\": \"Japanese officials speculate something must be terribly wrong in North Korea to make a\"}, {\"start\": 180.6, \"end\": 188.12, \"text\": \"fisherman so desperate he would travel that far, only to die before reaching land.\"}, {\"start\": 189.8, \"end\": 196.52, \"text\": \"If you've been suspecting that your older model iPhone has been slow lately,\"}, {\"start\": 196.64, \"end\": 198.48, \"text\": \"you are right.\"}, {\"start\": 198.48, \"end\": 207.68, \"text\": \"Today Apple admitted to slowing down older iPhones.\"}, {\"start\": 207.68, \"end\": 209.64, \"text\": \"The company says it is doing it because of battery problems.\"}, {\"start\": 209.64, \"end\": 213.2, \"text\": \"Older batteries can cause iPhones to shut down without warning.\"}, {\"start\": 213.24, \"end\": 219.76, \"text\": \"So to prevent that, the company reportedly says it has created software that manages\"}, {\"start\": 219.84, \"end\": 222.64, \"text\": \"batteries as they age.\"}, {\"start\": 222.92, \"end\": 234.16, \"text\": \"Apple says the iPhone S-E, iPhone 6, iPhone 6S and iPhone 7 are all impacted.\"}, {\"start\": 235.36, \"end\": 242.56, \"text\": \"Kensington Palace released the official engagement pictures of\"}, {\"start\": 242.56, \"end\": 249.92, \"text\": \"Prince Harry and Meghan Markle today.\"}, {\"start\": 249.92, \"end\": 252.32, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 252.32, \"end\": 253.88, \"text\": \"The couple first met last July.\"}, {\"start\": 253.88, \"end\": 257.36, \"text\": \"They were set up on a blind date by mutual friend.\"}, {\"start\": 257.36, \"end\": 259.76, \"text\": \"The couple announced their engagement last month.\"}, {\"start\": 259.76, \"end\": 268.0, \"text\": \"They are set to marry on May 19th at Windsor Castle.\"}, {\"start\": 268.0, \"end\": 280.28, \"text\": \"After that, they will live in Nottingham Cottage at Kensington Palace in London.\"}, {\"start\": 280.28, \"end\": 288.4, \"text\": \"The pair plans to spend Christmas with Queen Elizabeth and other members of the royal family.\"}, {\"start\": 290.12, \"end\": 293.08, \"text\": \"Today is the official start of the winter season.\"}, {\"start\": 293.08, \"end\": 298.96, \"text\": \"Forecasters say more than half a foot of snow will fall in northern New England, the northern\"}, {\"start\": 298.96, \"end\": 307.56, \"text\": \"Great Lakes and the northern Plains before the end of the week.\"}, {\"start\": 307.6, \"end\": 313.72, \"text\": \"Frigid temperatures are also expected in parts of the South over the next few days.\"}, {\"start\": 313.72, \"end\": 321.16, \"text\": \"Some areas are already getting snow and cold conditions, just as the holiday travel season begins.\"}, {\"start\": 321.24, \"end\": 329.12, \"text\": \"AAA predicts more than 107 million people are heading somewhere between now and the\"}, {\"start\": 329.12, \"end\": 332.28, \"text\": \"end of the year.\"}, {\"start\": 333.92, \"end\": 348.16, \"text\": \"Five-year-old Geneva Sambuchino from Cincinnati, Ohio is demonstrating the real spirit of Christmas.\"}, {\"start\": 348.16, \"end\": 356.12, \"text\": \"For the past two years she and her dad have been playing games at \\\"Dave and Busters\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 356.12, \"end\": 360.52, \"text\": \"and racking up winning tickets.\"}, {\"start\": 360.52, \"end\": 365.16, \"text\": \"But she's not spending the winning tickets on prizes for herself.\"}, {\"start\": 365.16, \"end\": 374.84, \"text\": \"She decided to buy Christmas toys for kids in need instead.\"}, {\"start\": 374.84, \"end\": 381.48, \"text\": \"When managers at \\\"Dave and Busters\\\" heard what Geneva was doing, they doubled her tickets\"}, {\"start\": 381.48, \"end\": 387.12, \"text\": \"to more than 100,000.\"}, {\"start\": 387.12, \"end\": 389.76, \"text\": \"That's a lot of toys!\"}, {\"start\": 391.92, \"end\": 394.2, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 394.2, \"end\": 395.5, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 395.5, \"end\": 398.28, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 398.28, \"end\": 403.56, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 403.56, \"end\": 410.12, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "URLsI7KVA70": {
    "video_id": "URLsI7KVA70",
    "title": "Deputy get into scuffle with suspect on highway (ASL - 3.19.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180320",
    "duration": 86,
    "view_count": 75,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.78, \"end\": 7.7, \"text\": \"A man is facing charges after he got into a scuffle with a Georgia deputy.\"}, {\"start\": 7.74, \"end\": 14.66, \"text\": \"The video we're about to show you shows the deputy trying to arrest a man during a traffic\"}, {\"start\": 14.66, \"end\": 17.82, \"text\": \"stop but he resists.\"}, {\"start\": 17.82, \"end\": 20.02, \"text\": \"The suspect and deputy began to struggle on the side of the road.\"}, {\"start\": 20.02, \"end\": 23.86, \"text\": \"The suspect is seen pushing the deputy down, jumping back in his car and driving away as\"}, {\"start\": 23.86, \"end\": 26.54, \"text\": \"the deputy tries to hang on to the vehicle.\"}, {\"start\": 26.56, \"end\": 29.28, \"text\": \"It was all caught on camera.\"}, {\"start\": 57.12, \"end\": 63.14, \"text\": \"According to the Sheriff's office, after the suspect drove away a passerby followed him\"}, {\"start\": 63.14, \"end\": 65.06, \"text\": \"until the deputy caught up.\"}, {\"start\": 65.06, \"end\": 70.94, \"text\": \"After a high-speed chase and several law enforcement cars damaged in the process, deputies were\"}, {\"start\": 70.94, \"end\": 74.22, \"text\": \"able to force the suspect off the road and arrest him.\"}, {\"start\": 74.22, \"end\": 79.08, \"text\": \"He faces assault and drug charges.\"}, {\"start\": 79.08, \"end\": 84.96, \"text\": \"The Sheriff's office says a large number of Xanax pills were found in the man's possession.\"}]"
  },
  "LPESvRATSxI": {
    "video_id": "LPESvRATSxI",
    "title": "Sign1News Virtual Chat: Rikki Poynter Deaf Influencer Spotlight  (w/closed caption)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20210509",
    "duration": 3296,
    "view_count": 1475,
    "description": "JOIN THE CONVERSATION: Sign1News spotlights Deaf social media influencers. Sign1News anchor Jethro Wooddall conducts an open, honest 1-on-1 discussion with Rikki Poynter.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase,live_chat",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 64.139, \"end\": 75.089, \"text\": \"Hello everyone welcome to Sign1News' live virtual chat I'm Jethro Wooddall we have a\"}, {\"start\": 75.089, \"end\": 83.009, \"text\": \"great show for you today you're going to enjoy it throughout the month of May Sign1News will\"}, {\"start\": 83.009, \"end\": 94.579, \"text\": \"be celebrating and spotlighting deaf social media influencers all over the world\"}, {\"start\": 94.579, \"end\": 107.09, \"text\": \"today's guest is an extremely popular vlogger if you don't know her you will know her after\"}, {\"start\": 107.09, \"end\": 115.319, \"text\": \"the show is over but before we get to our featured guest here's a quick look at some\"}, {\"start\": 115.319, \"end\": 128.319, \"text\": \"stories trending in the news today\"}, {\"start\": 128.319, \"end\": 135.449, \"text\": \"it's been over a year since the coronavirus pandemic started but health officials and\"}, {\"start\": 135.449, \"end\": 147.09, \"text\": \"scientists still have not given a definite explanation on how the virus is transmitted\"}, {\"start\": 147.09, \"end\": 157.599, \"text\": \"finally on Friday the centers for disease control and prevention website updated its\"}, {\"start\": 157.599, \"end\": 173.06, \"text\": \"explanations they are now emphasizing that the virus is spread through the air and inhalation\"}, {\"start\": 173.06, \"end\": 183.699, \"text\": \"is one of the main ways to contract the virus by standing close to someone who is infected\"}, {\"start\": 183.699, \"end\": 194.65, \"text\": \"and particles fly out to either land on your face or breathe into your mouth the CDC is\"}, {\"start\": 194.65, \"end\": 206.87, \"text\": \"placing less emphasis on the risk of picking it up from surfaces that people touch then\"}, {\"start\": 206.87, \"end\": 219.28, \"text\": \"touching their eyes nose or mouth health officials say the new CDC explanation does not change\"}, {\"start\": 219.28, \"end\": 226.84, \"text\": \"the recommended guidelines which include continuing to wear a mask social distancing washing your\"}, {\"start\": 226.84, \"end\": 241.209, \"text\": \"hands frequently and getting vaccinated\"}, {\"start\": 241.209, \"end\": 254.65, \"text\": \"apparently airline passengers are quite angry these days according to the Federal Aviation\"}, {\"start\": 254.65, \"end\": 266.05, \"text\": \"Administration in the past three months the agency has gotten about 1300 reports of unruly\"}, {\"start\": 266.05, \"end\": 279.97, \"text\": \"passengers the reports include people refusing to wear\"}, {\"start\": 279.97, \"end\": 296.34, \"text\": \"mandated masks passengers disturbing other passengers assaulting flight crews\"}, {\"start\": 296.34, \"end\": 309.419, \"text\": \"and drinking their own alcohol on flights and it's not just airplanes\"}, {\"start\": 309.419, \"end\": 320.319, \"text\": \"the TSA says it is approaching 2000 reports of travelers not complying with the federal\"}, {\"start\": 320.319, \"end\": 332.199, \"text\": \"mask mandate and that includes people on planes buses boats trains and in transportation hubs\"}, {\"start\": 332.199, \"end\": 349.669, \"text\": \"like airports and train stations what is going on\"}, {\"start\": 349.669, \"end\": 363.11, \"text\": \"last month the consumer product safety issued an urgent warning about the Peloton treadmill\"}, {\"start\": 363.11, \"end\": 380.379, \"text\": \"and requested a recall after one child died and 70 others were injured at the time officials\"}, {\"start\": 380.379, \"end\": 395.37, \"text\": \"with Peloton confirmed a child died but refused to issue a recall but earlier this week Peloton's\"}, {\"start\": 395.37, \"end\": 406.909, \"text\": \"CEO issued an apology and admitted it was a mistake to push back against the CPCS's\"}, {\"start\": 406.909, \"end\": 433.669, \"text\": \"request Peloton recalled all of its treadmills resulting in $165 million in lost sales\"}, {\"start\": 433.669, \"end\": 442.169, \"text\": \"a lot of nervous eyes will be looking into the sky this weekend scientists around the\"}, {\"start\": 442.169, \"end\": 451.08, \"text\": \"world are tracking an out-of-control Chinese rocket that is on a collision course with\"}, {\"start\": 451.08, \"end\": 463.209, \"text\": \"Earth it's expected to make landfall sometime in the next three days one problem no one\"}, {\"start\": 463.209, \"end\": 475.11, \"text\": \"is sure exactly where the rocket will land or when\"}, {\"start\": 475.11, \"end\": 487.629, \"text\": \"this is serious even the Pentagon is tracking the debris but they have no plans of shooting\"}, {\"start\": 487.629, \"end\": 500.259, \"text\": \"the rocket down because 70% of the Earth's surface\"}, {\"start\": 500.259, \"end\": 508.36, \"text\": \"is covered in water so scientists say there is little reason to panic unless of course\"}, {\"start\": 508.36, \"end\": 521.75, \"text\": \"the rocket is hurtling towards the backyard of someone living in the other 30% let's keep\"}, {\"start\": 521.75, \"end\": 533.61, \"text\": \"our fingers crossed for a splash landing versus a crash landing\"}, {\"start\": 533.61, \"end\": 546.42, \"text\": \"okay now let me introduce our guests today I am so excited to chat with her Ricky Poynter\"}, {\"start\": 546.42, \"end\": 559.42, \"text\": \"is one of the biggest and most popular social media influencers on the planet\"}, {\"start\": 559.42, \"end\": 574.899, \"text\": \"she is a content creator writer accessibility consultant and public speaker her blunt comedic\"}, {\"start\": 574.899, \"end\": 591.59, \"text\": \"and honest style of vlogging has garnered nearly 100,000 followers on YouTube's so welcome\"}, {\"start\": 591.59, \"end\": 603.22, \"text\": \"hi how are you I'm so excited to chat with you welcome welcome to Sign1News thank you\"}, {\"start\": 603.22, \"end\": 613.46, \"text\": \"for having me when you first started how did you know you wanted to do this it was really\"}, {\"start\": 613.46, \"end\": 623.31, \"text\": \"because I grew up in mainstream schools and the teachers would always say when you finish\"}, {\"start\": 623.31, \"end\": 635.24, \"text\": \"high school you go to college and get a job but I was deaf and it wasn't easy for me I\"}, {\"start\": 635.24, \"end\": 645.65, \"text\": \"didn't grow up using ASL I spoke I tried to learn ASL myself but it didn't stick because\"}, {\"start\": 645.65, \"end\": 658.88, \"text\": \"I didn't have anyone else to sign with so my hearing friend I was the only deaf person\"}, {\"start\": 658.88, \"end\": 664.42, \"text\": \"in my school maybe there was another deaf person anyway she was going to college and\"}, {\"start\": 664.42, \"end\": 671.92, \"text\": \"getting a job so I was trying to find employment too but they didn't want me I'm like why not\"}, {\"start\": 671.92, \"end\": 684.44, \"text\": \"me I'm deaf so I was trying and applying to schools and trying to figure how to do it\"}, {\"start\": 684.44, \"end\": 690.88, \"text\": \"but it was a challenge for me they were saying I was deaf and different but I didn't realize\"}, {\"start\": 690.88, \"end\": 707.101, \"text\": \"that until much later so I was watching a YouTube video on make-up and that was my first\"}, {\"start\": 707.101, \"end\": 712.3, \"text\": \"YouTube video and I was like wow that makeup video is nice and pretty interesting and I\"}, {\"start\": 712.3, \"end\": 718.83, \"text\": \"thought about I'll make a make-up video on YouTube and that was funny because I had never\"}, {\"start\": 718.83, \"end\": 732.0, \"text\": \"used make-up before but I was like I'll make a make-up vlog and that's how I got in the\"}, {\"start\": 732.0, \"end\": 740.26, \"text\": \"hole and wanted to know more so I was doing that for a few years and still couldn't get\"}, {\"start\": 740.26, \"end\": 751.41, \"text\": \"a job a normal job so I saw people making videos and blogs and making money from YouTube\"}, {\"start\": 751.41, \"end\": 762.001, \"text\": \"videos and maybe I want to work with you but the makeup thing wasn't working for me it\"}, {\"start\": 762.001, \"end\": 767.02, \"text\": \"was really expensive if you want to review products and you always had to buy buy buy\"}, {\"start\": 767.02, \"end\": 779.35, \"text\": \"it was really expensive but I didn't want to quit YouTube I was stily\"}, {\"start\": 779.35, \"end\": 790.0, \"text\": \"trying to apply for jobs but it didn't work so I dropped it decided I didn't want to do\"}, {\"start\": 790.0, \"end\": 792.863, \"text\": \"make up anymore I still liked makeup but I didn't want to make videos about it so I was\"}, {\"start\": 792.863, \"end\": 803.69, \"text\": \"thinking when I was doing the make-up videos they were interesting to watch and this was\"}, {\"start\": 803.69, \"end\": 812.57, \"text\": \"a long time ago when my hearing was a little better I still didn't get what they are saying\"}, {\"start\": 812.57, \"end\": 826.051, \"text\": \"then I was introduced to autocaptioning back then it was worse I remember those days when\"}, {\"start\": 826.051, \"end\": 840.44, \"text\": \"I first started I was watching a video on concealer okay sure I was watching but the\"}, {\"start\": 840.44, \"end\": 855.13, \"text\": \"captioning said zebra there is no zebra in concealer maybe it was like the differen colors\"}, {\"start\": 855.13, \"end\": 864.11, \"text\": \"of something I don't know and that's when I started captioning and I was like hey can\"}, {\"start\": 864.11, \"end\": 881.37, \"text\": \"you caption your videos make better captioning and YouTube was like no it was either no or\"}, {\"start\": 881.37, \"end\": 893.97, \"text\": \"just turn on the auto captioning so it just kept going and here I am so that auto captioning\"}, {\"start\": 893.97, \"end\": 901.89, \"text\": \"started you from then to where you are now know I can talk about access and when you\"}, {\"start\": 901.89, \"end\": 911.19, \"text\": \"are watching YouTube videos and finally learning deaf people can do it I am a deaf person obviously\"}, {\"start\": 911.19, \"end\": 924.5, \"text\": \"me too I didn't know it personally especially mainstreamed deaf people but if you watching\"}, {\"start\": 924.5, \"end\": 934.72, \"text\": \"YouTube and you see culturally deaf people which is really awesome but I couldn't really\"}, {\"start\": 934.72, \"end\": 943.32, \"text\": \"connect yes we were both deaf but I didn't know ASL I will still watch and be fascinated\"}, {\"start\": 943.32, \"end\": 955.81, \"text\": \"and want to learn more but what if another deaf kid who is mainstreamed want to see more\"}, {\"start\": 955.81, \"end\": 963.79, \"text\": \"from a deaf person like them so I started making videos about that the converging of\"}, {\"start\": 963.79, \"end\": 971.24, \"text\": \"access and deafness and then put it all together and again here I am right honestly sometimes\"}, {\"start\": 971.24, \"end\": 977.56, \"text\": \"you have to start with something and if that doesn't work then you find something that\"}, {\"start\": 977.56, \"end\": 986.85, \"text\": \"does work at the same time is teaching you how to improve and interact with other people\"}, {\"start\": 986.85, \"end\": 996.36, \"text\": \"yes like I was teaching and talking about my experience and learning from others and\"}, {\"start\": 996.36, \"end\": 1005.31, \"text\": \"trying to make friends changes everything now I have deaf friends I know more ASL I'm\"}, {\"start\": 1005.31, \"end\": 1010.93, \"text\": \"not fluent obviously but if you look at now compared to then it's night and day you're\"}, {\"start\": 1010.93, \"end\": 1018.56, \"text\": \"not the same person if I'm signing on line it's more awkward but if I'm communicating\"}, {\"start\": 1018.56, \"end\": 1027.179, \"text\": \"face-to-face yeah is little bit better and that's because my brain is not overthinking\"}, {\"start\": 1027.179, \"end\": 1037.589, \"text\": \"trying to sign on a video my brain is thinking too much I tell myself to relax but I can't\"}, {\"start\": 1037.589, \"end\": 1044.62, \"text\": \"I know it's hard because you can see yourself but you don't have someone on the other end\"}, {\"start\": 1044.62, \"end\": 1052.74, \"text\": \"to talk to if it's not perfect or something I don't like it's like agh stop stop yes I\"}, {\"start\": 1052.74, \"end\": 1063.54, \"text\": \"know the feeling I think you said you started like 2013 2012 yeah that's when I first started\"}, {\"start\": 1063.54, \"end\": 1072.11, \"text\": \"make-up videos in 2010 and then I switched over to deaf access that was around 2013 or\"}, {\"start\": 1072.11, \"end\": 1082.49, \"text\": \"2014 or somewhere around there okay I think maybe was a combination of the two anyway\"}, {\"start\": 1082.49, \"end\": 1092.99, \"text\": \"but for now you're focusing on when did you know that you have become and official social\"}, {\"start\": 1092.99, \"end\": 1099.809, \"text\": \"media influencer it's really funny because when you first sent me the question I thought\"}, {\"start\": 1099.809, \"end\": 1111.4, \"text\": \"I am not influencer I never use that word it's a weird word it's funny because when\"}, {\"start\": 1111.4, \"end\": 1131.36, \"text\": \"I think about an influencer I think about a top people that's always buying things but\"}, {\"start\": 1131.36, \"end\": 1140.73, \"text\": \"now that I'm thinking about it if influencer doesn't mean someone who makes money but influences\"}, {\"start\": 1140.73, \"end\": 1150.1, \"text\": \"people to start captioning videos or making other content accessible then okay I'm an\"}, {\"start\": 1150.1, \"end\": 1162.89, \"text\": \"influencer it's a weird word really honestly it's an English word only it's really weird\"}, {\"start\": 1162.89, \"end\": 1173.43, \"text\": \"I think it's because sometimes people are like okay I hate influencer it's always so\"}, {\"start\": 1173.43, \"end\": 1181.61, \"text\": \"whatever I guess you known when the first person started\"}, {\"start\": 1181.61, \"end\": 1193.13, \"text\": \"captioning videos and another YouTuber named Tyler Oakley in 2015 started making videos\"}, {\"start\": 1193.13, \"end\": 1203.02, \"text\": \"about captioning to support mine that changed everything and more people started captioning\"}, {\"start\": 1203.02, \"end\": 1218.28, \"text\": \"videos I would say in 2015 is when you made ripples when you started making noise yeah\"}, {\"start\": 1218.28, \"end\": 1226.37, \"text\": \"in 2015 that's when it first started taking off because someone at the top at YouTube\"}, {\"start\": 1226.37, \"end\": 1234.2, \"text\": \"said something because before 2015 it was just little old me oh I see from your perspective\"}, {\"start\": 1234.2, \"end\": 1242.32, \"text\": \"back then you were not that popular but now you are you know that right the biggest most\"}, {\"start\": 1242.32, \"end\": 1258.03, \"text\": \"popular influencer oh come on dont' be shy about that hi Roseline thank you thank you\"}, {\"start\": 1258.03, \"end\": 1269.95, \"text\": \"thank you thank you of course I know you're a big influencer maybe I can use a different\"}, {\"start\": 1269.95, \"end\": 1284.97, \"text\": \"sign that that it is easy or hard being an influencer it's kind of in the middle\"}, {\"start\": 1284.97, \"end\": 1292.05, \"text\": \"I think it's hard to answer okay that's fair I don't know if it's really easy i don't know\"}, {\"start\": 1292.05, \"end\": 1307.42, \"text\": \"hi Martha it can be hard I think people think that it's really easy to make videos say hi\"}, {\"start\": 1307.42, \"end\": 1314.41, \"text\": \"and then put it out there and that's it but no you really have to edit first before you\"}, {\"start\": 1314.41, \"end\": 1318.86, \"text\": \"record anything you have to think about what I'm going to make how you're going to make\"}, {\"start\": 1318.86, \"end\": 1326.559, \"text\": \"it then you have to edit it and if you're me you have to listen to it and that's hard\"}, {\"start\": 1326.559, \"end\": 1338.39, \"text\": \"when you're deaf I hear something but I don't understand and they have make sure it's good\"}, {\"start\": 1338.39, \"end\": 1346.1, \"text\": \"because it is not good no one is going to watch then you have to record what people\"}, {\"start\": 1346.1, \"end\": 1359.559, \"text\": \"what am I saying then you have to worry about what people are saying what people are saying\"}, {\"start\": 1359.559, \"end\": 1373.29, \"text\": \"behind closed doors my phone my bad that can be hard and everything you put out people\"}, {\"start\": 1373.29, \"end\": 1386.13, \"text\": \"will see what they see they don't know everything that happened off camera but at the same time\"}, {\"start\": 1386.13, \"end\": 1399.66, \"text\": \"if someone sees it and someone finally can relate that's a good thing is it easy or hard\"}, {\"start\": 1399.66, \"end\": 1407.21, \"text\": \"it's somewhere in the middle I guess it depends on the day depends on the video content overall\"}, {\"start\": 1407.21, \"end\": 1418.46, \"text\": \"it can be in the middle that's sometimes I have really great awesome days like I said\"}, {\"start\": 1418.46, \"end\": 1428.77, \"text\": \"if for example there was a conference on video playlists\"}, {\"start\": 1428.77, \"end\": 1436.66, \"text\": \"yes sorry I can't fingerspell right now and they were talking on the panel about the workshop\"}, {\"start\": 1436.66, \"end\": 1444.98, \"text\": \"and people were coming up to me mostly deaf people kids and they said hi I'm so happy\"}, {\"start\": 1444.98, \"end\": 1458.22, \"text\": \"to see you and meet you you know that's the easy good part it's both it's both really\"}, {\"start\": 1458.22, \"end\": 1464.6, \"text\": \"the minute you started in the social media world it was completely different now everyone's\"}, {\"start\": 1464.6, \"end\": 1475.072, \"text\": \"watching and judging the whole thing I get it people think it's so easy or you\"}, {\"start\": 1475.072, \"end\": 1492.57, \"text\": \"make a lot of money I'm like no that would be nice but no it's a lot of work still it\"}, {\"start\": 1492.57, \"end\": 1507.091, \"text\": \"does help so I can't complain ok just a little bit of course when you do social media do\"}, {\"start\": 1507.091, \"end\": 1512.62, \"text\": \"you have some parts of the social media world where you're proud of the work and some parts\"}, {\"start\": 1512.62, \"end\": 1519.24, \"text\": \"you not-really proud of you know the positive and the negative what is the part you are\"}, {\"start\": 1519.24, \"end\": 1534.28, \"text\": \"most proud of maybe there are a few well first if there is captioning and they say I started\"}, {\"start\": 1534.28, \"end\": 1547.14, \"text\": \"captioning because of you if it's one person that's just one more person than before that's\"}, {\"start\": 1547.14, \"end\": 1565.23, \"text\": \"good also I'm thinking of of sorry or if another kid another young deaf child and other young\"}, {\"start\": 1565.23, \"end\": 1572.58, \"text\": \"people sometimes they are the deaf person they know they grew up in a hearing world\"}, {\"start\": 1572.58, \"end\": 1578.581, \"text\": \"or family they are in mainstream schools and they say they're so happy I saw your video\"}, {\"start\": 1578.581, \"end\": 1586.28, \"text\": \"you helped me so much because I realize being deaf is not bad yes access barriers make it\"}, {\"start\": 1586.28, \"end\": 1591.78, \"text\": \"hard sometimes but before when I was a kid I hated being deaf because I was only deaf\"}, {\"start\": 1591.78, \"end\": 1599.21, \"text\": \"person well my mom was deaf too and went to mainstream schools and she voiced we don't\"}, {\"start\": 1599.21, \"end\": 1609.36, \"text\": \"have the best relationship so if I changed my mindset of another deaf kid or person I'm\"}, {\"start\": 1609.36, \"end\": 1617.58, \"text\": \"happy to help someone build their self-esteem that's great that's good for the moment I\"}, {\"start\": 1617.58, \"end\": 1626.78, \"text\": \"agree it's a point where we can really give someone a positive perspective and yes this\"}, {\"start\": 1626.78, \"end\": 1634.29, \"text\": \"is the wonderful part of being deaf that's a plus and they start to learn ASL to family\"}, {\"start\": 1634.29, \"end\": 1645.32, \"text\": \"and friends to help with their identity I'm like yes yes yes same so that's the part you're\"}, {\"start\": 1645.32, \"end\": 1652.96, \"text\": \"most proud of conversely what part of being a social media influencer do you just hate\"}, {\"start\": 1652.96, \"end\": 1663.04, \"text\": \"and being in that world I have already talked about that part of my life about people not\"}, {\"start\": 1663.04, \"end\": 1673.79, \"text\": \"knowing what goes on behind closed doors like people saying she's not deaf she uses her\"}, {\"start\": 1673.79, \"end\": 1679.74, \"text\": \"voice she's not deaf she's not signing she's not deaf sometimes if I'm signing in the video\"}, {\"start\": 1679.74, \"end\": 1693.041, \"text\": \"I know I'm not fluent I know I'm not the best signer I know that already I know that I don't\"}, {\"start\": 1693.041, \"end\": 1699.02, \"text\": \"have a vast vocabulary grew up in a hearing what are you doing in a hearing world Elaine\"}, {\"start\": 1699.02, \"end\": 1708.29, \"text\": \"hi I'm reading the comments as well hello everyone thank you for commenting so far I\"}, {\"start\": 1708.29, \"end\": 1713.679, \"text\": \"want to engage with the audience of course people are like you're not deaf if I sign\"}, {\"start\": 1713.679, \"end\": 1721.669, \"text\": \"sometimes people are like I can't understand what you're saying stop signing talk I'm like\"}, {\"start\": 1721.669, \"end\": 1729.7, \"text\": \"okay but if I don't sign in the video then people say why did you stop signing why are\"}, {\"start\": 1729.7, \"end\": 1742.6, \"text\": \"you not signing I don't know what to do so I keep trying but for me English is my first\"}, {\"start\": 1742.6, \"end\": 1756.95, \"text\": \"language I'm fluent in English so yeah it makes editing harder because I'm like what\"}, {\"start\": 1756.95, \"end\": 1766.85, \"text\": \"did I say but now I stream when I edit sometimes so viewers will help me edit so if I can't\"}, {\"start\": 1766.85, \"end\": 1777.97, \"text\": \"understand myself or lip read they will help me it's hard people are like she's not deaf\"}, {\"start\": 1777.97, \"end\": 1792.22, \"text\": \"and they tease my signing someone was like have you had an audio test not all deaf people\"}, {\"start\": 1792.22, \"end\": 1801.429, \"text\": \"are the same you're right I remember 5 or 6 years ago when I first started on Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 1801.429, \"end\": 1809.74, \"text\": \"I mostly posted on Facebook I would post something and there would be complaints in the comments\"}, {\"start\": 1809.74, \"end\": 1822.27, \"text\": \"and now I'm like was like like this morning\"}, {\"start\": 1822.27, \"end\": 1833.34, \"text\": \"yes I'm deaf I'm deaf you can ask my audiologist I don't know what you want me to say sorry\"}, {\"start\": 1833.34, \"end\": 1842.29, \"text\": \"I'm sorry my signing is not perfect I'm trying what's important is that you still finding\"}, {\"start\": 1842.29, \"end\": 1851.44, \"text\": \"your identity of course everyone knows deafness runs the spectrum different signing styles\"}, {\"start\": 1851.44, \"end\": 1868.25, \"text\": \"cultural different test qualities so diverse it's not just one level yeah I agree with\"}, {\"start\": 1868.25, \"end\": 1874.99, \"text\": \"that I agree with that right you're still deaf the next day when you wake up you're\"}, {\"start\": 1874.99, \"end\": 1887.039, \"text\": \"still deaf I know everyone doesn't like me I'm okay with that but it's just when it's\"}, {\"start\": 1887.039, \"end\": 1898.99, \"text\": \"personal it's deflating it's nice to have tough skin and not feel easily offended it\"}, {\"start\": 1898.99, \"end\": 1907.88, \"text\": \"would be nice but we are human so if someone criticizes us I grew up in an abusive home\"}, {\"start\": 1907.88, \"end\": 1921.2, \"text\": \"so it's personal for me I understand that sucks I'm sorry but now that's in the past\"}, {\"start\": 1921.2, \"end\": 1931.01, \"text\": \"now I know I've seen a couple of videos one of them was about your carpal tunnel syndrome\"}, {\"start\": 1931.01, \"end\": 1938.95, \"text\": \"first of all that's not fun I experienced that myself it is not fun for a deaf person\"}, {\"start\": 1938.95, \"end\": 1947.571, \"text\": \"to have carpal tunnel what were your emotions when you realize you still have to blogging\"}, {\"start\": 1947.571, \"end\": 1958.95, \"text\": \"and you've got carpal tunnel syndrome so I'm not surprised that I have it since I've been\"}, {\"start\": 1958.95, \"end\": 1965.43, \"text\": \"using it since I was kid also when I started gaming streaming everyday for three years\"}, {\"start\": 1965.43, \"end\": 1975.429, \"text\": \"I'm sorry time out every day for three years yes I was using it every day but then when\"}, {\"start\": 1975.429, \"end\": 1997.4, \"text\": \"I started streaming almost everyday for three years so was a lot it was a lot\"}, {\"start\": 1997.4, \"end\": 2006.58, \"text\": \"so most of it is in my left hand I write with my left I sign with my right I can't sign\"}, {\"start\": 2006.58, \"end\": 2023.57, \"text\": \"with my left hand I tried but it's weird, awkward so at first I was working and I was\"}, {\"start\": 2023.57, \"end\": 2031.409, \"text\": \"like crap and then I have a little bit in my right hand just a little bit but mostly\"}, {\"start\": 2031.409, \"end\": 2047.5, \"text\": \"my left is where it hurts now it's getting better knock on wood it's getting better well\"}, {\"start\": 2047.5, \"end\": 2065.599, \"text\": \"my last name is Wooddall don't hurt yourself I was worried because when I was first diagnosed\"}, {\"start\": 2065.599, \"end\": 2071.96, \"text\": \"with carpal tunnel syndrome it was just in my left hand but then because I switched to\"}, {\"start\": 2071.96, \"end\": 2080.99, \"text\": \"my right hand it started in my right hand as well not as bad as in my left not the same\"}, {\"start\": 2080.99, \"end\": 2096.01, \"text\": \"level as the left but still I started worrying like oh great I don't have a language again\"}, {\"start\": 2096.01, \"end\": 2110.92, \"text\": \"how will people understand me if I can't sign if I can't use it\"}, {\"start\": 2110.92, \"end\": 2118.24, \"text\": \"I was diagnosed in July and I really wanted to start making more ASL videos just for practice\"}, {\"start\": 2118.24, \"end\": 2132.2, \"text\": \"but it was a problem I was crying saying what am I going to do and everything just got worse\"}, {\"start\": 2132.2, \"end\": 2142.16, \"text\": \"but now it's okay yes Elaine finger spelling finger spelling is already the most difficult\"}, {\"start\": 2142.16, \"end\": 2150.94, \"text\": \"thing for me every time I try to figure spell my hands get all jumbled up so with carpal\"}, {\"start\": 2150.94, \"end\": 2160.223, \"text\": \"tunnel syndrom it's so hard why much respect to you and for people going through CTS I\"}, {\"start\": 2160.223, \"end\": 2168.68, \"text\": \"went through it and I never want to experience it again it was like that show switched at\"}, {\"start\": 2168.68, \"end\": 2184.71, \"text\": \"birth I understand when the mother couldn't sign because of CTS I get it speaking of no\"}, {\"start\": 2184.71, \"end\": 2190.92, \"text\": \"go ahead II remember I didn't sign for a few months well I did sym-com streaming at first\"}, {\"start\": 2190.92, \"end\": 2199.599, \"text\": \"I was on a panel with who was it oh yeah convo for gamers it was the first time I was signing\"}, {\"start\": 2199.599, \"end\": 2214.719, \"text\": \"for a live panel for everyone to see it was the first time in months i was nervous but\"}, {\"start\": 2214.719, \"end\": 2224.319, \"text\": \"it was fine of course I know you want to sign a lot with carpal tunnel but what do you do\"}, {\"start\": 2224.319, \"end\": 2229.029, \"text\": \"if you're having a bad day sometimes it's like what am I trying to say the brain and\"}, {\"start\": 2229.029, \"end\": 2240.769, \"text\": \"hands don't connect yeah my brain and my hands don't connect all the time they're not friends\"}, {\"start\": 2240.769, \"end\": 2253.239, \"text\": \"I feel you I feel you since you brought up switched at birth let's talk about camisado\"}, {\"start\": 2253.239, \"end\": 2267.799, \"text\": \"and working with my coworker Martha Anger tell me about your work basically she was\"}, {\"start\": 2267.799, \"end\": 2276.029, \"text\": \"acting in the show and I was like it's weird to explain I was sort of an interpreter but\"}, {\"start\": 2276.029, \"end\": 2280.24, \"text\": \"not really I'm not an interpreter just to make that clear I am not an interpreter I\"}, {\"start\": 2280.24, \"end\": 2296.069, \"text\": \"want to let the audience know I'm not an interpreter but when the director wanted someone to help\"}, {\"start\": 2296.069, \"end\": 2306.38, \"text\": \"speak to Martha while she was acting she can read lips but I can't okay that's interesting\"}, {\"start\": 2306.38, \"end\": 2315.079, \"text\": \"you can hear and speak but you can't read lips a little bit it is a skill but for the\"}, {\"start\": 2315.079, \"end\": 2320.109, \"text\": \"most part if someone is new and starts talking to me I don't understand a word they're saying\"}, {\"start\": 2320.109, \"end\": 2327.63, \"text\": \"to me if I know the person it's little bit easier but Martha is a phenomenal lip reader\"}, {\"start\": 2327.63, \"end\": 2343.549, \"text\": \"but she doesn't voice but I can so it was a great collaboration so if the director said\"}, {\"start\": 2343.549, \"end\": 2352.339, \"text\": \"something to me and I didn't understand Martha would interpret for me what the director was\"}, {\"start\": 2352.339, \"end\": 2361.7, \"text\": \"saying but if she wanted to say or sign something to the director she would sign and I would\"}, {\"start\": 2361.7, \"end\": 2373.099, \"text\": \"speak to the director so we were kind of both interpreters air quote interpreters really\"}, {\"start\": 2373.099, \"end\": 2379.71, \"text\": \"technically deaf people already have kind of an internal ability to facilitate communication\"}, {\"start\": 2379.71, \"end\": 2390.539, \"text\": \"in a way we are interpreters I would help with her lines and another person in the scene\"}, {\"start\": 2390.539, \"end\": 2399.519, \"text\": \"would have to sign a little bit too so we would change the lines so Martha would be\"}, {\"start\": 2399.519, \"end\": 2412.95, \"text\": \"like sign it this way or that way to fit better it was great teamwork\"}, {\"start\": 2412.95, \"end\": 2419.17, \"text\": \"sometimes that just happens and it makes the dream work I'm sorry that's my boss that's\"}, {\"start\": 2419.17, \"end\": 2425.746, \"text\": \"an awesome picture of the three of you that was after we had been filming all day and\"}, {\"start\": 2425.746, \"end\": 2435.369, \"text\": \"it was over they wrapped up filming we were ready for bed and we were like we are finished\"}, {\"start\": 2435.369, \"end\": 2449.009, \"text\": \"that's awesome I bet that was a lot of fun I'm trying to see if I finished all the questions\"}, {\"start\": 2449.009, \"end\": 2458.869, \"text\": \"okay so you as a social media influencer or as\"}, {\"start\": 2458.869, \"end\": 2468.191, \"text\": \"yourself what is your best advice and words of encouragement for your fans who watch and\"}, {\"start\": 2468.191, \"end\": 2480.059, \"text\": \"love you what your best advice I got a few but first of all you don't need a fancy camera\"}, {\"start\": 2480.059, \"end\": 2501.229, \"text\": \"a cell phone your first video will probably suck ouch but see what I mean she's blunt\"}, {\"start\": 2501.229, \"end\": 2511.509, \"text\": \"and honest my first few videos were awful if you use an editor you will be fine but\"}, {\"start\": 2511.509, \"end\": 2519.029, \"text\": \"if you've never done YouTube video before or whatever maybe don't know what to do that's\"}, {\"start\": 2519.029, \"end\": 2540.92, \"text\": \"fine don't worry about it just make the video\"}, {\"start\": 2540.92, \"end\": 2547.549, \"text\": \"and put it out there dont' worry I'm taking notes you're taking notes good you're a good\"}, {\"start\": 2547.549, \"end\": 2552.469, \"text\": \"student thank you sometimes a lot of people are worried that people may not like what\"}, {\"start\": 2552.469, \"end\": 2558.279, \"text\": \"they're doing I don't care just make whatever you want if you want to make a funny video\"}, {\"start\": 2558.279, \"end\": 2566.9, \"text\": \"do it or talk about captioning sometimes people are worried about well another deaf person\"}, {\"start\": 2566.9, \"end\": 2574.459, \"text\": \"or person with a disability in general has already made a video like this so your experience\"}, {\"start\": 2574.459, \"end\": 2588.339, \"text\": \"there are many diverse deaf people on YouTube and Facebook you're still on YouTube or Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 2588.339, \"end\": 2599.16, \"text\": \"make the video talk about whatever have fun don't worry about it and caption of course\"}, {\"start\": 2599.16, \"end\": 2612.549, \"text\": \"that's for everyone hearing people especially did you get that hearing people\"}, {\"start\": 2612.549, \"end\": 2622.4, \"text\": \"sometimes I will make of vlog and I vacillate on whether to post it or not I understand\"}, {\"start\": 2622.4, \"end\": 2626.799, \"text\": \"I've been doing this for 10 years more than 10 years almost 11 years and I still go hello\"}, {\"start\": 2626.799, \"end\": 2637.089, \"text\": \"everybody welcome again hello everybody welcome but hello funding the 10th time is like hello\"}, {\"start\": 2637.089, \"end\": 2647.289, \"text\": \"which hello do I like best that no no no no ooh I like that hello best wow the sun just\"}, {\"start\": 2647.289, \"end\": 2656.359, \"text\": \"came in really bright that's fine it takes practice so the first few videos may suck\"}, {\"start\": 2656.359, \"end\": 2666.4, \"text\": \"but don't worry about it just practice you learn and then you get better and you don't\"}, {\"start\": 2666.4, \"end\": 2680.049, \"text\": \"need a fancy editor just basic editing and I put it out there that's it\"}, {\"start\": 2680.049, \"end\": 2685.92, \"text\": \"sometimes people see the you tubers have fancy editing and casting it I know you use your\"}, {\"start\": 2685.92, \"end\": 2694.42, \"text\": \"phone in your videos and you also use the phone for editing too no I use a camera a\"}, {\"start\": 2694.42, \"end\": 2706.349, \"text\": \"Canon M50 for videos and sometimes I use my cell phone for broll sometimes I use my cell\"}, {\"start\": 2706.349, \"end\": 2711.93, \"text\": \"phone for that most of the time I'm using the camera it depends on where I am if I'm\"}, {\"start\": 2711.93, \"end\": 2724.959, \"text\": \"traveling I don't want to lug all of that stuff with me I have a small camera as well\"}, {\"start\": 2724.959, \"end\": 2732.979, \"text\": \"I know some people edit with their phones I can't I respect that I've tried and tried\"}, {\"start\": 2732.979, \"end\": 2744.789, \"text\": \"but it's so small I need your big equipment big technology yeah i mean right now you don't\"}, {\"start\": 2744.789, \"end\": 2758.829, \"text\": \"need to add to your CTS i tried to edit on tiktok I know now it's a new set up for captioning\"}, {\"start\": 2758.829, \"end\": 2769.78, \"text\": \"but before you had to yeah I had to type it myself and make it stay on the time line it\"}, {\"start\": 2769.78, \"end\": 2783.349, \"text\": \"was hard I used tiktok I don't know if you used tiktok\"}, {\"start\": 2783.349, \"end\": 2790.37, \"text\": \"also as a deaf person I would finish signing and I still have to type in the words and\"}, {\"start\": 2790.37, \"end\": 2794.759, \"text\": \"upload them hearing people they just talk into the phone when they finished hit a button\"}, {\"start\": 2794.759, \"end\": 2800.119, \"text\": \"listen for the playback and the captioning is already set up if they make a mistake they\"}, {\"start\": 2800.119, \"end\": 2809.519, \"text\": \"can just type in the changes when are deaf people going to get it easy they have technology\"}, {\"start\": 2809.519, \"end\": 2820.079, \"text\": \"that translates the captioning please someone make technology for us thank you those are\"}, {\"start\": 2820.079, \"end\": 2832.349, \"text\": \"fighting words I'm just saying I'm all for that we're all advocating for captioning and\"}, {\"start\": 2832.349, \"end\": 2844.099, \"text\": \"access it's time for everybody okay thank you for chatting with me do you have any last\"}, {\"start\": 2844.099, \"end\": 2856.509, \"text\": \"wrods for we move on I may have a project I can't really talk a lot about because it's\"}, {\"start\": 2856.509, \"end\": 2873.41, \"text\": \"not on my channel but my friend Jake Roper has a channel called Vsauce3 he is making\"}, {\"start\": 2873.41, \"end\": 2896.95, \"text\": \"a lot of science to see if you can survive it's like sci-fi movies like a quiet place\"}, {\"start\": 2896.95, \"end\": 2909.88, \"text\": \"I love a quiet place you know the monster or the movie alien or back to the future you\"}, {\"start\": 2909.88, \"end\": 2929.589, \"text\": \"know when Marty had the big sonic boom how do you sign that you know all that science\"}, {\"start\": 2929.589, \"end\": 2938.329, \"text\": \"stuff well he survived that and went back to the 1980's or something but in real life\"}, {\"start\": 2938.329, \"end\": 2950.24, \"text\": \"you can't survive that you would probably die I would be the first one to die you would\"}, {\"start\": 2950.24, \"end\": 2966.76, \"text\": \"probably die it's all of that science stuff you helped me understand so we have an episode\"}, {\"start\": 2966.76, \"end\": 2984.699, \"text\": \"called a quiet place or a quiet place episode maybe it may be released this month or June\"}, {\"start\": 2984.699, \"end\": 2995.67, \"text\": \"maybe maybe so people if you're interested in that kind of thing go to her page and find\"}, {\"start\": 2995.67, \"end\": 3005.68, \"text\": \"out it's not on my channel but I will share it all shared on Twitter or whatever go find\"}, {\"start\": 3005.68, \"end\": 3017.449, \"text\": \"out on her social media maybe maybe not thank you so much for chatting with me today thank\"}, {\"start\": 3017.449, \"end\": 3029.831, \"text\": \"you and now before we go don't forget this is can anyone\"}, {\"start\": 3029.831, \"end\": 3039.959, \"text\": \"guess Mother's Day weekend and this is my early happy Mother's Day greetings to my awesome\"}, {\"start\": 3039.959, \"end\": 3050.69, \"text\": \"mother she is awesome really I could go on and on\"}, {\"start\": 3050.69, \"end\": 3068.339, \"text\": \"and on about my mom she is my number one fan she loves me I'm so blessed to be her son\"}, {\"start\": 3068.339, \"end\": 3079.319, \"text\": \"I love you mom you're the best you the most caring loving king generous I just love you\"}, {\"start\": 3079.319, \"end\": 3090.449, \"text\": \"love you thank you all apparently people are shelling out big dollars for dear old mom\"}, {\"start\": 3090.449, \"end\": 3099.89, \"text\": \"this weekend the National retail Federation says Mother's Day's spending is expected to\"}, {\"start\": 3099.89, \"end\": 3120.68, \"text\": \"total $28 billion that's more than one billion dollars from 2020 wow to all of you moms my\"}, {\"start\": 3120.68, \"end\": 3130.809, \"text\": \"mom included to all of the mothers you deserve it from all of us here at Sign1News happy\"}, {\"start\": 3130.809, \"end\": 3145.119, \"text\": \"Mother's Day to mothers everywhere so we would like to end the show with words of inspiration\"}, {\"start\": 3145.119, \"end\": 3158.2, \"text\": \"words that will hopefully help you dream a little bigger aim a little higher and find\"}, {\"start\": 3158.2, \"end\": 3170.489, \"text\": \"the courage to be a little bolder this quote comes from an unknown author it says cry if\"}, {\"start\": 3170.489, \"end\": 3193.14, \"text\": \"needed slow down if needed reevaluate if needed\"}, {\"start\": 3193.14, \"end\": 3213.17, \"text\": \"take a break if needed talk to someone if needed\"}, {\"start\": 3213.17, \"end\": 3229.759, \"text\": \"but you'll never see the reward if you quit keep going and most importantly never give\"}, {\"start\": 3229.759, \"end\": 3239.559, \"text\": \"up on yourself thank you again to our amazing guest Rikki\"}, {\"start\": 3239.559, \"end\": 3249.859, \"text\": \"Poynter I thoroughly enjoyed our chat thank you to our viewers and of course to our loyal\"}, {\"start\": 3249.859, \"end\": 3263.5, \"text\": \"app subscribers you help make this broadcast happen be sure to join us next Saturday at\"}, {\"start\": 3263.5, \"end\": 3276.91, \"text\": \"6 PM Eastern time for another great live virtual chat\"}, {\"start\": 3276.91, \"end\": 3284.169, \"text\": \"have a great weekend happy Mother's Day mom I love you good night\"}]"
  },
  "3kaUiON2fS8": {
    "video_id": "3kaUiON2fS8",
    "title": "Here’s what you missed at 258 Deaf Street (ASL - 10.15.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20181016",
    "duration": 326,
    "view_count": 90,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.76, \"end\": 7.12, \"text\": \"As you know the 258 Street Deaf festival was in Atlanta this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 7.12, \"end\": 11.92, \"text\": \"It was a big success and lots of fun!\"}, {\"start\": 11.92, \"end\": 20.8, \"text\": \"Thousands of people showed up at the Georgia International Convention Center.\"}, {\"start\": 20.8, \"end\": 33.6, \"text\": \"Sign1News anchor Crystal Cousineau and multimedia journalist Martha Anger were there as well,\"}, {\"start\": 33.68, \"end\": 38.28, \"text\": \"capturing all the excitement.\"}, {\"start\": 42.28, \"end\": 44.8, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 44.8, \"end\": 51.04, \"text\": \"Obviously you can see I'm at 258 Deaf Street.\"}, {\"start\": 51.04, \"end\": 55.04, \"text\": \"I've been here all day, walking around, getting a feel for the event, stopping by the different\"}, {\"start\": 55.04, \"end\": 61.04, \"text\": \"vendors' tables and meeting a lot of people.\"}, {\"start\": 61.04, \"end\": 66.32, \"text\": \"I love it, especially seeing so many Deaf people walking around.\"}, {\"start\": 66.32, \"end\": 68.2, \"text\": \"Want to see what it looks like inside?\"}, {\"start\": 68.2, \"end\": 69.96, \"text\": \"This way.\"}, {\"start\": 71.04, \"end\": 75.76, \"text\": \"The first thing you saw were table after table of Deaf-friendly businesses and vendors set\"}, {\"start\": 75.76, \"end\": 83.2, \"text\": \"up to inform and entertain.\"}, {\"start\": 83.2, \"end\": 89.39, \"text\": \"Thousands of people showed up, waiting in anxious anticipation for the show to begin.\"}, {\"start\": 89.39, \"end\": 95.27, \"text\": \"Wow we talked about coming to Atlanta, what it would look like and the expectations, and\"}, {\"start\": 95.27, \"end\": 97.07, \"text\": \"boy oh boy!\"}, {\"start\": 97.08, \"end\": 101.6, \"text\": \"When we got here, you guys were so warm and inviting, so friendly and sociable.\"}, {\"start\": 101.6, \"end\": 104.64, \"text\": \"Now I understand the concept of Southern hospitality.\"}, {\"start\": 104.64, \"end\": 120.68, \"text\": \"The crowd was wowed by an amazing magic show.\"}, {\"start\": 120.68, \"end\": 131.04, \"text\": \"Then the crowd enjoyed the smooth moves of former Deaf Got Talent winner Joey Antonio.\"}, {\"start\": 131.04, \"end\": 135.08, \"text\": \"Deafies In Drag brought fabulous drama and comedy just before the Deaf Got Talent competition\"}, {\"start\": 135.08, \"end\": 136.56, \"text\": \"began.\"}, {\"start\": 136.56, \"end\": 144.48, \"text\": \"Sonibert showcased her ASL storytelling skills by becoming several characters.\"}, {\"start\": 144.48, \"end\": 150.28, \"text\": \"Angelo gave a powerfully dramatic interpretation of a Deaf man being bound in the hearing world.\"}, {\"start\": 150.28, \"end\": 156.56, \"text\": \"BeBe Beautiful signed and danced.\"}, {\"start\": 156.56, \"end\": 163.36, \"text\": \"Hpnoti'Q's performance was about being bold, direct and speaking the truth.\"}, {\"start\": 163.36, \"end\": 168.96, \"text\": \"Sharia danced in honor of a Deaf woman battling breast cancer.\"}, {\"start\": 169.0, \"end\": 172.28, \"text\": \"Finally it was up to the judges to pick a winner.\"}, {\"start\": 178.28, \"end\": 181.36, \"text\": \"BeBe beautiful won the Deaf Got Talent competition and the $1,000 winner's check.\"}, {\"start\": 189.84, \"end\": 192.08, \"text\": \"The reason I came here is because of you guys.\"}, {\"start\": 192.08, \"end\": 194.36, \"text\": \"The Deaf community needs this.\"}, {\"start\": 194.36, \"end\": 199.08, \"text\": \"We need this kind of collaboration with so many diverse Deaf people coming together.\"}, {\"start\": 199.08, \"end\": 200.26, \"text\": \"It's heartwarming.\"}, {\"start\": 200.26, \"end\": 201.94, \"text\": \"And the night was over.\"}, {\"start\": 201.94, \"end\": 204.34, \"text\": \"258 Deaf Street was a success.\"}, {\"start\": 204.34, \"end\": 214.24, \"text\": \"Wow 258 Deaf Street was an all day event.\"}, {\"start\": 214.24, \"end\": 219.54, \"text\": \"Now let's wrap it up. How do you feel?\"}, {\"start\": 223.52, \"end\": 225.14, \"text\": \"It's a blessing, a real blessing to have the amazing Deaf community come here where we\"}, {\"start\": 225.14, \"end\": 228.32, \"text\": \"all share our identity and ASL culture.\"}, {\"start\": 228.32, \"end\": 231.28, \"text\": \"It's so beautiful. It feels like family.\"}, {\"start\": 236.32, \"end\": 238.32, \"text\": \"This Atlanta community -- wow!\"}, {\"start\": 238.32, \"end\": 241.84, \"text\": \"I feel so welcomed, it's mind blowing.\"}, {\"start\": 241.84, \"end\": 245.36, \"text\": \"I want to see this in every state.\"}, {\"start\": 250.66, \"end\": 254.72, \"text\": \"It's an honor to be here to see so many diverse people with so much talent.\"}, {\"start\": 254.72, \"end\": 256.98, \"text\": \"Thank you. I'm grateful as well.\"}, {\"start\": 261.92, \"end\": 263.74, \"text\": \"Yeah I feel so blessed and grateful for the Atlanta community.\"}, {\"start\": 263.74, \"end\": 265.78, \"text\": \"You believed in us and we believe in you.\"}, {\"start\": 265.78, \"end\": 266.42, \"text\": \"Don't give up.\"}, {\"start\": 266.42, \"end\": 267.04, \"text\": \"That's important.\"}, {\"start\": 267.04, \"end\": 268.2, \"text\": \"Don't give up.\"}, {\"start\": 273.78, \"end\": 275.52, \"text\": \"I think everyone will agree with me on this.\"}, {\"start\": 275.52, \"end\": 280.04, \"text\": \"We would not be here were it not for the Deaf community.\"}, {\"start\": 280.04, \"end\": 284.68, \"text\": \"This community drew us all together and it's nice to give back to the community to show\"}, {\"start\": 284.68, \"end\": 288.16, \"text\": \"that it's really about them.\"}, {\"start\": 288.16, \"end\": 289.7, \"text\": \"Today was a beautiful day.\"}, {\"start\": 289.92, \"end\": 294.38, \"text\": \"Atlanta is warm and friendly and like I said, now I know what Southern hospitality looks like.\"}, {\"start\": 301.22, \"end\": 303.0, \"text\": \"Yeah I agree. Surprisingly Atlanta has such a positive attitude.\"}, {\"start\": 303.0, \"end\": 307.96, \"text\": \"I never felt so welcomed and the talent was shocking and awe-inspiring.\"}, {\"start\": 307.96, \"end\": 310.74, \"text\": \"They created their own music with their voice.\"}, {\"start\": 310.74, \"end\": 312.14, \"text\": \"I was like \\\"What!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 312.14, \"end\": 313.3, \"text\": \"I never saw that before.\"}, {\"start\": 313.3, \"end\": 317.36, \"text\": \"That's why I'm excited and hope to work with them in the future.\"}, {\"start\": 317.44, \"end\": 319.84, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 319.84, \"end\": 321.96, \"text\": \"Our life.\"}, {\"start\": 321.96, \"end\": 325.56, \"text\": \"Our language.\"}]"
  },
  "5zfPLAz4l-Q": {
    "video_id": "5zfPLAz4l-Q",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.17.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171218",
    "duration": 406,
    "view_count": 474,
    "description": "December 17, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-MASSIVE POWER OUTAGE SHUTS DOWN ATLANTA AIRPORT\n-SENATORS TO INTRODUCE CYBER THREAT BILL\n-POLICE ARREST EX-WIFE FOR NBA STAR'S MURDER\n-NEW CREW BLASTS OFF TO INTERNATIONAL SPACE STATION\n-WEEKEND BOX OFFICE\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE Our talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CN",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.12, \"end\": 7.04, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.12, \"end\": 8.62, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.62, \"end\": 9.96, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 10.0, \"end\": 12.4, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.84, \"end\": 22.54, \"text\": \"Thousands of passengers were stranded at Atlanta's Hartsfield-Jackson International airport today\"}, {\"start\": 22.54, \"end\": 27.72, \"text\": \"due to a massive power outage.\"}, {\"start\": 27.76, \"end\": 36.32, \"text\": \"The Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) stopped all planes from landing\"}, {\"start\": 36.32, \"end\": 39.46, \"text\": \"and grounded departing planes at their gates.\"}, {\"start\": 39.46, \"end\": 48.14, \"text\": \"Incoming international flights were diverted to other airports.\"}, {\"start\": 48.2, \"end\": 57.16, \"text\": \"There were a few backup generators operating but that only provided dim sources of light.\"}, {\"start\": 57.16, \"end\": 61.52, \"text\": \"There were reports of people having a hard time making calls on their cell phones because\"}, {\"start\": 61.52, \"end\": 67.62, \"text\": \"so many people were trying to make calls at the same time.\"}, {\"start\": 67.64, \"end\": 73.78, \"text\": \"Power crews worked feverishly to restore power.\"}, {\"start\": 73.78, \"end\": 81.34, \"text\": \"Hartsfield Jackson is the busiest airport in the world.\"}, {\"start\": 81.34, \"end\": 90.38, \"text\": \"It handles about 2,500 flights and roughly 275,000 passengers daily.\"}, {\"start\": 90.38, \"end\": 98.12, \"text\": \"Aviation officials say a power outage this size at this airport will have ripple effects\"}, {\"start\": 98.12, \"end\": 106.4, \"text\": \"on air traffic all over the country and the world.\"}, {\"start\": 106.4, \"end\": 113.06, \"text\": \"Airport officials have not yet given a cause for the fire.\"}, {\"start\": 115.68, \"end\": 127.88, \"text\": \"Republican Senator James Lankford of Oklahoma says a bipartisan group of senators will introduce\"}, {\"start\": 127.88, \"end\": 139.6, \"text\": \"legislation early next week designed to battle international cyber threats.\"}, {\"start\": 139.6, \"end\": 150.92, \"text\": \"The goal is to improve communication between federal intelligence agencies and state election\"}, {\"start\": 150.92, \"end\": 157.44, \"text\": \"officials to stem foreign intervention in elections.\"}, {\"start\": 157.44, \"end\": 174.56, \"text\": \"Republican Lindsay Graham and Democrats Amy Klobuchar and Kamala Harris\"}, {\"start\": 174.56, \"end\": 177.48, \"text\": \"are supporting the bill.\"}, {\"start\": 177.48, \"end\": 184.82, \"text\": \"It comes in the wake of Russia's meddling in the 2016 elections.\"}, {\"start\": 187.7, \"end\": 200.72, \"text\": \"Police in Memphis have arrested this woman Sherra Wright-Robinson\"}, {\"start\": 200.72, \"end\": 205.04, \"text\": \"in connection with her ex-husband's death.\"}, {\"start\": 205.04, \"end\": 213.82, \"text\": \"Her ex-husband was former NBA player Lorenzen Wright.\"}, {\"start\": 213.82, \"end\": 228.159, \"text\": \"In 2010 his bullet-riddled body was found in a swampy field outside Memphis.\"}, {\"start\": 228.16, \"end\": 235.72, \"text\": \"Earlier in the day a 9-1-1 call was made from Wright's phone\"}, {\"start\": 235.78, \"end\": 240.36, \"text\": \"but all the operator heard was gunfire.\"}, {\"start\": 240.36, \"end\": 247.46, \"text\": \"The 9-1-1 center did not report the call to police until several days later.\"}, {\"start\": 247.46, \"end\": 253.76, \"text\": \"Wright-Robinson has been charged with first-degree murder and\"}, {\"start\": 253.76, \"end\": 258.64, \"text\": \"conspiracy with another man to kill her ex-husband.\"}, {\"start\": 258.68, \"end\": 265.94, \"text\": \"Police did not say what led them to make the arrest and\"}, {\"start\": 265.94, \"end\": 271.8, \"text\": \"did not provide a motive for the killing.\"}, {\"start\": 271.88, \"end\": 279.48, \"text\": \"But they did say more people will be charged in Wright's murder.\"}, {\"start\": 282.32, \"end\": 288.98, \"text\": \"Three astronauts representing the US, Russia and Japan on their way\"}, {\"start\": 288.98, \"end\": 293.7, \"text\": \"to the International Space Station.\"}, {\"start\": 293.7, \"end\": 297.76, \"text\": \"The Soyuz capsule launched from the space complex in Kazakhstan Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 297.76, \"end\": 300.92, \"text\": \"The trip is expected to take about two days.\"}, {\"start\": 300.92, \"end\": 312.12, \"text\": \"They are scheduled to dock at the space station early Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 312.12, \"end\": 315.04, \"text\": \"The crew will join others already at the ISS.\"}, {\"start\": 315.04, \"end\": 325.84, \"text\": \"They will spend roughly 4 months in space, conducting more than 200 science investigations\"}, {\"start\": 325.84, \"end\": 335.84, \"text\": \"in fields like biology, earth science, human research and technology development.\"}, {\"start\": 338.48, \"end\": 341.56, \"text\": \"Here's a quick recap of this weekend's top box office movies.\"}, {\"start\": 341.68, \"end\": 350.84, \"text\": \"No surprise...\\\"Star Wars: The Last Jedi\\\" decimated the competition with\"}, {\"start\": 350.84, \"end\": 356.48, \"text\": \"estimated weekend receipts reaching $220 mllion.\"}, {\"start\": 356.48, \"end\": 362.72, \"text\": \"When international receipts are factored in, \\\"The Last Jedi\\\" made $450 million in one weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 362.84, \"end\": 372.36, \"text\": \"The animated comedy \\\"Ferdinand\\\" finished a distant second -- taking in $13.3 million.\"}, {\"start\": 372.36, \"end\": 382.6, \"text\": \"The animated musical \\\"Coco\\\" slid from 1st to 3rd place with $10 million.\"}, {\"start\": 385.24, \"end\": 387.36, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 387.4, \"end\": 388.44, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 388.46, \"end\": 390.48, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 390.52, \"end\": 394.44, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 394.44, \"end\": 400.02, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "RzWDyJd5A4Y": {
    "video_id": "RzWDyJd5A4Y",
    "title": "Barking dog saves family’s life (ASL - 1.12.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180113",
    "duration": 63,
    "view_count": 226,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.78, \"end\": 14.62, \"text\": \"A Missouri family is lucky to be alive and it's all thanks to their dog.\"}, {\"start\": 14.62, \"end\": 19.02, \"text\": \"Matt Beaudreau says he woke up around 2 AM to the sound of his dog, River, barking.\"}, {\"start\": 19.02, \"end\": 28.62, \"text\": \"He got up, took River out to do her business and went back to sleep.\"}, {\"start\": 28.62, \"end\": 33.34, \"text\": \"Fifteen minutes later, River started barking again.\"}, {\"start\": 33.34, \"end\": 38.12, \"text\": \"That's when they discovered an intense fire raging inside the family's garage.\"}, {\"start\": 38.12, \"end\": 42.86, \"text\": \"They quickly gathered their three kids and the dogs and got out of the house.\"}, {\"start\": 42.86, \"end\": 47.54, \"text\": \"The fire went through the garage wall and burned down the front porch.\"}, {\"start\": 47.64, \"end\": 55.68, \"text\": \"Beaudreau says they have working smoke detectors in the home but it was River's heroic actions\"}, {\"start\": 55.68, \"end\": 61.16, \"text\": \"that save the family from the tragedy.\"}]"
  },
  "uMYeyplfXw8": {
    "video_id": "uMYeyplfXw8",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.22.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171123",
    "duration": 453,
    "view_count": 211,
    "description": "November 22, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-GABBY DOUGLAS SAYS SHE WAS ABUSED BY TEAM DOCTOR\n-ZIMBABWE CELEBRATES MNANGAGWA'S RETURN\n-FIRST FAMILY THANKSGIVING IN W. PALM BEACH \n-GUN SELLERS EXPECT BLACK FRIDAY BREAK FROM TRUMP SLUMP\n-HEAVIEST MAN UNDERGOES SECOND SURGERY\n-COST OF THANKSGIVING DINNER LOWEST IN 5 YEARS\n-HOW YOUR FOOD IS ENGINEERED TO TASTE GOOD\n-DAD ROCKS TUTU AT DAUGHTER'S BALLET CLASS\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFE",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.62, \"end\": 12.78, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I'm Jethro Wooddall. Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.92, \"end\": 16.28, \"text\": \"U.S. Olympic gymnast\"}, {\"start\": 16.42, \"end\": 23.06, \"text\": \"Gabby Douglas released a statement on Instagram Tuesday\"}, {\"start\": 23.2, \"end\": 32.48, \"text\": \"revealing that she was abused by her team's former doctor Larry Nassar.\"}, {\"start\": 32.88, \"end\": 37.12, \"text\": \"She said she had not previously shared her experiences publicly because\"}, {\"start\": 37.68, \"end\": 43.52, \"text\": \"Nassar's victims were conditioned to stay silent\"}, {\"start\": 43.6, \"end\": 48.64, \"text\": \"and because her experiences were very painful.\"}, {\"start\": 48.64, \"end\": 53.04, \"text\": \"In the statement Douglas commented on abuse allegations made by other gymnasts,\"}, {\"start\": 53.04, \"end\": 62.08, \"text\": \"including her teammate Aly Raisman.\"}, {\"start\": 63.04, \"end\": 70.8, \"text\": \"And she apologized for a previous tweet that was widely viewed as victim shaming.\"}, {\"start\": 71.68, \"end\": 77.6, \"text\": \"Hundred and 25 women have accused Nassar of sexual misconduct.\"}, {\"start\": 78.24, \"end\": 79.84, \"text\": \"Nassar was in court today.\"}, {\"start\": 79.84, \"end\": 85.52, \"text\": \"He pleaded guilty to multiple charges of sexual assault.\"}, {\"start\": 88.56, \"end\": 93.28, \"text\": \"People in Zimbabwe are still dancing in the streets.\"}, {\"start\": 93.28, \"end\": 104.0, \"text\": \"Last night they were celebrating the resignation of long time president Robert Mugabe.\"}, {\"start\": 104.64, \"end\": 112.88, \"text\": \"Today they were celebrating the return of former vice president Emerson Mnangagwa.\"}, {\"start\": 113.12, \"end\": 116.56, \"text\": \"He will be the country's next president.\"}, {\"start\": 116.56, \"end\": 121.76, \"text\": \"He fled about two weeks ago after Mugabe fired him.\"}, {\"start\": 121.76, \"end\": 128.24, \"text\": \"That would trigger Mugabe's downfall.\"}, {\"start\": 128.24, \"end\": 134.24, \"text\": \"Mnangagwa is expected to be sworn in on Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 135.36, \"end\": 139.328, \"text\": \"On Tuesday the First Family took a break from Washington DC\"}, {\"start\": 139.328, \"end\": 142.96, \"text\": \"to celebrate Thanksgiving in West Palm Beach, Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 142.96, \"end\": 152.64, \"text\": \"The Trumps will spend six days at his private club Mar-A-Lago.\"}, {\"start\": 153.2, \"end\": 158.56, \"text\": \"Originally Trump was only going to stay for five days but decided to extend his vacation one more day.\"}, {\"start\": 158.56, \"end\": 161.52, \"text\": \"They will leave to head back to Washington, DC on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 161.84, \"end\": 168.88, \"text\": \"Trump supporters are tentatively planning a \\\"Welcome Home Mr. President\\\" rally on Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 169.84, \"end\": 174.16, \"text\": \"U.S. gun dealers are hoping Black Friday\"}, {\"start\": 174.16, \"end\": 177.04, \"text\": \"means a lot of green for their bottom line.\"}, {\"start\": 177.04, \"end\": 180.24, \"text\": \"Gun sales were strong last year on Black Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 180.24, \"end\": 182.88, \"text\": \"But gun sales have since snagged\"}, {\"start\": 182.88, \"end\": 185.44, \"text\": \"in part due to President Trump's election\"}, {\"start\": 185.44, \"end\": 190.24, \"text\": \"and the prospect of tighter gun control laws dissipating.\"}, {\"start\": 190.24, \"end\": 197.92, \"text\": \"Two top gun manufacturers, Remington and Browning,\"}, {\"start\": 197.92, \"end\": 201.52, \"text\": \"hope to bounce back this Black Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 201.52, \"end\": 209.2, \"text\": \"They are offering rebates of up to $200 for shotguns\"}, {\"start\": 209.2, \"end\": 214.0, \"text\": \"and $100 for rifles.\"}, {\"start\": 214.08, \"end\": 221.36, \"text\": \"Retailer Cabela's is offering two weeks of deals on\"}, {\"start\": 221.36, \"end\": 223.84, \"text\": \"weapons and ammo, with Thanksgiving\"}, {\"start\": 223.84, \"end\": 227.84, \"text\": \"discounts up to half off.\"}, {\"start\": 227.84, \"end\": 235.2, \"text\": \"And other companies plan to offer discounts on line for cyber Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 236.96, \"end\": 239.808, \"text\": \"Juan Pedro used to weigh 1300 pounds\"}, {\"start\": 239.84, \"end\": 248.24, \"text\": \"and was once considered the heaviest man in the world.\"}, {\"start\": 248.72, \"end\": 252.64, \"text\": \"But a year ago the 32-year-old lost 440 pounds\"}, {\"start\": 252.64, \"end\": 258.64, \"text\": \"thanks to the intervention of a team of physicians in Mexico.\"}, {\"start\": 259.12, \"end\": 261.44, \"text\": \"Today Pedro underwent a second surgery\"}, {\"start\": 261.44, \"end\": 264.24, \"text\": \"to help them achieve a healthy weight.\"}, {\"start\": 264.24, \"end\": 266.16, \"text\": \"Pedro acknowledged that he's scared.\"}, {\"start\": 266.16, \"end\": 270.56, \"text\": \"But the medical team is prepared and optimistic.\"}, {\"start\": 270.56, \"end\": 274.56, \"text\": \"However, doctors advise that there are risks\"}, {\"start\": 274.56, \"end\": 280.48, \"text\": \"for patients with a high degree of obesity.\"}, {\"start\": 281.92, \"end\": 284.96, \"text\": \"A new report says eating on Thanksgiving\"}, {\"start\": 284.96, \"end\": 289.92, \"text\": \"will be a little cheaper this year.\"}, {\"start\": 290.24, \"end\": 296.88, \"text\": \"The American Farm Bureau Federation says\"}, {\"start\": 296.88, \"end\": 304.96, \"text\": \"the estimated average price of a traditional Thanksgiving dinner is $.75 cheaper.\"}, {\"start\": 305.28, \"end\": 307.68, \"text\": \"It says for a group of 10, dinner will cost\"}, {\"start\": 307.68, \"end\": 309.6, \"text\": \"around $49 this year\"}, {\"start\": 309.6, \"end\": 311.44, \"text\": \"or just under five dollars per person.\"}, {\"start\": 311.44, \"end\": 313.84, \"text\": \"The decline in price is due mainly\"}, {\"start\": 313.84, \"end\": 317.52, \"text\": \"to the declining cost of turkey.\"}, {\"start\": 319.28, \"end\": 323.12, \"text\": \"Ever wonder why your taste buds\"}, {\"start\": 323.12, \"end\": 326.72, \"text\": \"react to certain foods the way they do?\"}, {\"start\": 326.72, \"end\": 330.8, \"text\": \"Why you love a certain candy bar or\"}, {\"start\": 330.8, \"end\": 333.84, \"text\": \"a favorite brand of chips?\"}, {\"start\": 333.84, \"end\": 336.88, \"text\": \"According to scientists a lot of the foods we eat\"}, {\"start\": 336.88, \"end\": 341.76, \"text\": \"are engineered to taste great.\"}, {\"start\": 341.84, \"end\": 346.72, \"text\": \"The role of these chemists or \\\"flavorists\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 346.72, \"end\": 357.2, \"text\": \"is to formulate the taste in virtually every product we eat and drink that is\"}, {\"start\": 357.2, \"end\": 362.56, \"text\": \"processed, preserved or packaged before it hits store shelves.\"}, {\"start\": 362.72, \"end\": 366.32, \"text\": \"Some flavors contain only a single ingredient.\"}, {\"start\": 366.32, \"end\": 369.52, \"text\": \"Others may contain hundreds.\"}, {\"start\": 369.52, \"end\": 374.16, \"text\": \"The average is about 25 to 30 ingredients.\"}, {\"start\": 374.4, \"end\": 380.08, \"text\": \"The goal is to formulate a taste like mother nature intended.\"}, {\"start\": 380.32, \"end\": 383.28, \"text\": \"But to also re-create natural flavors and\"}, {\"start\": 383.28, \"end\": 388.08, \"text\": \"experiment with developing fantasy flavors as well.\"}, {\"start\": 389.36, \"end\": 393.36, \"text\": \"A good dad would do just about anything for his daughter.\"}, {\"start\": 393.68, \"end\": 396.64, \"text\": \"Here is a good example.\"}, {\"start\": 396.64, \"end\": 405.92, \"text\": \"Thanh Tran of Knoxville Tennessee showed off some fancy footwork at his daughter's ballet class.\"}, {\"start\": 405.92, \"end\": 409.12, \"text\": \"It was \\\"Bring Your Parents to Class\\\" day.\"}, {\"start\": 409.44, \"end\": 413.2, \"text\": \"Tran's wife is 7 months pregnant and couldn't participate.\"}, {\"start\": 413.2, \"end\": 415.811, \"text\": \"So the daring dad donned a tutu\"}, {\"start\": 415.84, \"end\": 419.12, \"text\": \"and did what he had to do.\"}, {\"start\": 419.12, \"end\": 428.08, \"text\": \"Video of Tran's performance is racking up thousands of views on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 430.0, \"end\": 433.36, \"text\": \"And those your top stories. I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 433.36, \"end\": 435.36, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 435.36, \"end\": 438.88, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 438.88, \"end\": 444.24, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "pYHNX1K_nLQ": {
    "video_id": "pYHNX1K_nLQ",
    "title": "What happened to the Tesla shot into space? (ASL 2.10.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180210",
    "duration": 76,
    "view_count": 205,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.24, \"end\": 19.48, \"text\": \"On Tuesday Space-X launched a red sports car into orbit with a mannequin named \\\"Starman\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 19.48, \"end\": 21.9, \"text\": \"behind the wheel.\"}, {\"start\": 21.9, \"end\": 30.0, \"text\": \"But where exactly is the car going?\"}, {\"start\": 30.0, \"end\": 44.36, \"text\": \"NASA's jet propulsion laboratory expects \\\"Starman\\\" to take this path as he orbits the sun.\"}, {\"start\": 44.36, \"end\": 53.719, \"text\": \"The farthest he'll get is about 155 million miles from the sun.\"}, {\"start\": 53.719, \"end\": 60.42, \"text\": \"That's about the same distance as Mars gets from the sun.\"}, {\"start\": 60.42, \"end\": 71.9, \"text\": \"Experts say the current projections could change, as forces such as radiation could\"}, {\"start\": 71.9, \"end\": 74.94, \"text\": \"slowly steer the roadster onto a different course.\"}]"
  },
  "41FOWmQsKPI": {
    "video_id": "41FOWmQsKPI",
    "title": "Dr. G. answers your questions: What is the cause of death for Covid-19?",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200416",
    "duration": 95,
    "view_count": 263,
    "description": "Posted 4.16.20",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en-US",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.829, \"end\": 5.72, \"text\": \"The next question is from Lonnie Overstreet.\"}, {\"start\": 5.72, \"end\": 15.69, \"text\": \"He wants to know when people die from Covid-19, what exactly is the cause of death?\"}, {\"start\": 15.69, \"end\": 21.26, \"text\": \"First you have to remember Covid-19 is the disease.\"}, {\"start\": 21.26, \"end\": 29.38, \"text\": \"If someone has coronavirus, not everyone will become sick.\"}, {\"start\": 29.38, \"end\": 36.61, \"text\": \"If you become sick, the illness itself is Covid-19.\"}, {\"start\": 36.61, \"end\": 49.379, \"text\": \"That means the infection has gotten into the lungs and overwhelmed the lungs with infection.\"}, {\"start\": 49.38, \"end\": 55.82, \"text\": \"When that happens it makes it harder and harder to breathe.\"}, {\"start\": 55.82, \"end\": 83.98, \"text\": \"And that can lead to other illnesses like ARDS which stands for acute respiratory distress syndrome.\"}, {\"start\": 83.99, \"end\": 90.36, \"text\": \"That's when people usually need ventilator support to breathe.\"}, {\"start\": 90.36, \"end\": 94.3, \"text\": \"We hope they don't die but sometimes they do.\"}]"
  },
  "p9jDq5hO7k8": {
    "video_id": "p9jDq5hO7k8",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.26.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180127",
    "duration": 607,
    "view_count": 1769,
    "description": "1.26.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-20 White House staffers interviewed in Russia probe\n-Cosby lawyers file motion to dismiss sex assault charges\n-Shoppers fight over Nutella \n-Reba Mcentire first woman to play KFC Colonel Sanders\n-How to defend yourself against the flu\n-Olympic sisters compete under different flags\n-Deaf school ribbon cutting for state of the art facility \n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, p",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.88, \"end\": 7.1, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.1, \"end\": 8.78, \"text\": \"Welcome Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.78, \"end\": 10.02, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 10.04, \"end\": 12.96, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.9, \"end\": 22.16, \"text\": \"The investigation into Russia's involvement in the 2016 election is expanding and involving\"}, {\"start\": 22.16, \"end\": 27.92, \"text\": \"more White House officials and aides than many people realized.\"}, {\"start\": 27.92, \"end\": 34.5, \"text\": \"President Trump's lawyers say 20 White House staffers have now sat for voluntary interviews\"}, {\"start\": 34.5, \"end\": 41.44, \"text\": \"with Special Counsel Robert Mueller.\"}, {\"start\": 41.44, \"end\": 50.6, \"text\": \"The administration says it has turned over more than 20,000 pages of documents.\"}, {\"start\": 50.66, \"end\": 57.06, \"text\": \"Trump says he is willing, in fact eager, to be next to be interviewed.\"}, {\"start\": 57.06, \"end\": 60.56, \"text\": \"But his lawyers say not so fast.\"}, {\"start\": 60.56, \"end\": 71.4, \"text\": \"CNN has learned it would be a sitdown meeting rather than written questions.\"}, {\"start\": 71.48, \"end\": 77.96, \"text\": \"And the range of interview topics would largely focused on possible obstruction of justice\"}, {\"start\": 77.96, \"end\": 91.6, \"text\": \"by asking the president if he asked former FBI director James Comey to drop the investigation\"}, {\"start\": 91.6, \"end\": 95.16, \"text\": \"into former National Security Advisor Michael Flynn.\"}, {\"start\": 95.16, \"end\": 97.94, \"text\": \"Trump has repeatedly deny those allegations.\"}, {\"start\": 97.94, \"end\": 104.58, \"text\": \"In addition, investigators want to learn more about the president's outreach to intelligence\"}, {\"start\": 104.58, \"end\": 111.3, \"text\": \"leaders about the Russia investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 114.64, \"end\": 122.62, \"text\": \"Attorneys for Bill Cosby are looking to have sexual assault charges against the comedian\"}, {\"start\": 122.62, \"end\": 124.4, \"text\": \"dismissed.\"}, {\"start\": 124.4, \"end\": 133.42, \"text\": \"Time magazine reports Cosby's legal team filed a motion Thursday, alleging misconduct by\"}, {\"start\": 133.42, \"end\": 137.58, \"text\": \"prosecutors and lack of proof.\"}, {\"start\": 137.58, \"end\": 146.88, \"text\": \"Cosby is scheduled to be retried in April on aggravated indecent assault charges.\"}, {\"start\": 146.88, \"end\": 158.46, \"text\": \"He's accused of drugging and assaulting a woman at his home more than a decade ago.\"}, {\"start\": 158.46, \"end\": 168.6, \"text\": \"The first trial ended in a mistrial when jurors could not agree on a unanimous verdict.\"}, {\"start\": 168.7, \"end\": 177.66, \"text\": \"Dozens of women have accused Cosby of sexual misconduct spanning decades.\"}, {\"start\": 177.76, \"end\": 180.16, \"text\": \"The comedian has denied every allegation against him.\"}, {\"start\": 183.2, \"end\": 192.96, \"text\": \"When a French supermarket chain discounted the chocolatey spread Nutella by 70 percent,\"}, {\"start\": 192.96, \"end\": 195.92, \"text\": \"shoppers went crazy trying to scoop up a jar.\"}, {\"start\": 196.24, \"end\": 203.68, \"text\": \"Chaotic scenes like this one were reported at several stores.\"}, {\"start\": 203.68, \"end\": 208.94, \"text\": \"Right after the supermarket opened its doors, people rushed to the Nutella pots, banging\"}, {\"start\": 208.94, \"end\": 210.34, \"text\": \"on each other.\"}, {\"start\": 210.34, \"end\": 212.76, \"text\": \"Video posted online showed people shoving, pushing and punching just to get their hands\"}, {\"start\": 212.76, \"end\": 215.58, \"text\": \"on the spread.\"}, {\"start\": 215.58, \"end\": 218.48, \"text\": \"The manager eventually had to call police.\"}, {\"start\": 220.8, \"end\": 231.48, \"text\": \"Kentucky Fried Chicken's iconic Colonel Sanders wears a white suit, black tie, glasses, white\"}, {\"start\": 231.48, \"end\": 235.88, \"text\": \"wig and goatee.\"}, {\"start\": 235.96, \"end\": 245.04, \"text\": \"Grammy award-winning country singer Reba McEntire is now the latest celebrity -- and the first\"}, {\"start\": 245.04, \"end\": 250.0, \"text\": \"woman -- to play Colonel Sanders.\"}, {\"start\": 250.0, \"end\": 256.88, \"text\": \"It's part of KFC's newest campaign promoting its Smoky Mountain barbecue fried chicken.\"}, {\"start\": 257.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"McEntire said she accepted the offer to play Colonel Sanders because she's a big fan of\"}, {\"start\": 261.2, \"end\": 266.48, \"text\": \"KFC's chicken and because she thought it was a great spoof.\"}, {\"start\": 266.64, \"end\": 273.2, \"text\": \"The commercials will start airing this Sunday and will run until April.\"}, {\"start\": 276.36, \"end\": 290.88, \"text\": \"The flu is hitting people really hard this year.\"}, {\"start\": 290.88, \"end\": 302.12, \"text\": \"Some places are even running short of the drug that helps minimize flu symptoms.\"}, {\"start\": 302.12, \"end\": 307.84, \"text\": \"So your best defense is you.\"}, {\"start\": 307.84, \"end\": 309.72, \"text\": \"Here are some suggestions on how to protect yourself.\"}, {\"start\": 309.72, \"end\": 322.12, \"text\": \"Stay away from too much sugar and alcohol.\"}, {\"start\": 322.12, \"end\": 338.28, \"text\": \"It can suppress your immune system.\"}, {\"start\": 338.28, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"Disinfect common areas in your home because the flu virus can live on surfaces for several\"}, {\"start\": 354.2, \"end\": 355.68, \"text\": \"hours.\"}, {\"start\": 355.68, \"end\": 365.4, \"text\": \"Wash those bedsheets, blankets, towels and your hands.\"}, {\"start\": 365.4, \"end\": 374.72, \"text\": \"And even though the flu season is well underway, it's not too late to get vaccinated.\"}, {\"start\": 374.72, \"end\": 381.68, \"text\": \"Experts recommend everyone six months of age and older get a flu shot.\"}, {\"start\": 384.2, \"end\": 391.96, \"text\": \"Two sisters from Minnesota will be competing in next month's winter Olympics.\"}, {\"start\": 392.16, \"end\": 399.88, \"text\": \"But they will be representing different countries.\"}, {\"start\": 400.2, \"end\": 408.56, \"text\": \"Marissa Brandt was born in South Korea but was adopted by American parents in 1992 when\"}, {\"start\": 408.68, \"end\": 413.36, \"text\": \"she was four months old.\"}, {\"start\": 413.36, \"end\": 418.24, \"text\": \"The Brandt's already had a daughter, Hannah, who was about the same age as Marissa.\"}, {\"start\": 418.24, \"end\": 420.48, \"text\": \"The girls instantly became best friends.\"}, {\"start\": 420.48, \"end\": 432.72, \"text\": \"So when Hannah switch from figure skating to ice hockey, Marissa did too.\"}, {\"start\": 432.72, \"end\": 436.32, \"text\": \"Both would go on to play ice hockey in college and now both will represent their home country\"}, {\"start\": 436.32, \"end\": 438.6, \"text\": \"in the Olympics.\"}, {\"start\": 438.6, \"end\": 445.04, \"text\": \"Hannah will represent the United States and Marissa will represent Korea.\"}, {\"start\": 445.12, \"end\": 449.36, \"text\": \"The girls say it's a dream come true.\"}, {\"start\": 449.36, \"end\": 455.16, \"text\": \"There is a very slim chance the United States and Korea will face each other in the Olympics.\"}, {\"start\": 455.16, \"end\": 460.44, \"text\": \"But the girls say if by some miracle it happens, it would be the perfect ending to their Olympic\"}, {\"start\": 460.44, \"end\": 465.08, \"text\": \"story.\"}, {\"start\": 467.28, \"end\": 472.28, \"text\": \"It was an exciting day at Atlanta Area School for the Deaf.\"}, {\"start\": 472.44, \"end\": 481.16, \"text\": \"Today students, staff and members from the Department of Education celebrated the ribbon-cutting\"}, {\"start\": 481.36, \"end\": 486.76, \"text\": \"for the school's new $75,000 state of the art greenhouse.\"}, {\"start\": 486.76, \"end\": 491.36, \"text\": \"The project took three years to complete.\"}, {\"start\": 491.36, \"end\": 499.12, \"text\": \"AASD is the first state school to build an industry-standard greenhouse, which will enhance\"}, {\"start\": 499.36, \"end\": 513.16, \"text\": \"the schools STEAM curriculum -- science, technology, engineering, arts and math.\"}, {\"start\": 513.16, \"end\": 520.32, \"text\": \"In a few months, the greenhouse will be filled with plants, flowers and fish.\"}, {\"start\": 520.32, \"end\": 527.96, \"text\": \"It will teach students the science behind plants, farming and landscaping and be incorporated\"}, {\"start\": 527.96, \"end\": 532.68, \"text\": \"in the school's food science and nutritional services programs.\"}, {\"start\": 532.68, \"end\": 538.12, \"text\": \"Several students say they already have plans to use what they learn to advance their careers\"}, {\"start\": 538.2, \"end\": 541.72, \"text\": \"after graduation.\"}, {\"start\": 541.72, \"end\": 546.92, \"text\": \"(Isamara Garcia) I want to become a veterinarian one day.\"}, {\"start\": 546.92, \"end\": 552.08, \"text\": \"I know it's going to be hard but I love interacting with animals.\"}, {\"start\": 552.08, \"end\": 555.8, \"text\": \"Also I enjoy grooming animals.\"}, {\"start\": 555.8, \"end\": 561.04, \"text\": \"My ultimate goal is to become a vet.\"}, {\"start\": 561.04, \"end\": 565.44, \"text\": \"(Shar Banbe) My goal is to become a florist.\"}, {\"start\": 565.44, \"end\": 573.68, \"text\": \"I want to make floral arrangements for Valentine's Day, weddings, funerals, romantic dates and\"}, {\"start\": 573.68, \"end\": 577.84, \"text\": \"birthdays.\"}, {\"start\": 577.84, \"end\": 583.44, \"text\": \"(Cameron Jones) I want to become an agricultural scientist and botanist.\"}, {\"start\": 585.56, \"end\": 587.92, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 587.92, \"end\": 589.2, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 589.2, \"end\": 591.32, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 591.32, \"end\": 595.44, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 595.44, \"end\": 601.08, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "70ddmjZLtJw": {
    "video_id": "70ddmjZLtJw",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.29.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180330",
    "duration": 476,
    "view_count": 1014,
    "description": "3.29.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Parkland shooter receives fan mail, donations\n-Stephon Clark funeral, more protests expected\n-Russia expels U.S. diplomats in retaliation\n-Boy in viral photo missing after crash\n-45 years ago final US ground troops leave Vietnam\n-1st case of super-resistant gonorrhea reported\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have background",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.2, \"end\": 9.8, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.8, \"end\": 12.34, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.34, \"end\": 13.9, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 13.9, \"end\": 17.2, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 21.06, \"end\": 36.62, \"text\": \"Authorities say Parkland, Florida shooter Nikolas Cruz is actually receiving fan mail.\"}, {\"start\": 36.7, \"end\": 41.26, \"text\": \"Hundreds of letters are coming in from all over the US and Europe from young girls, women\"}, {\"start\": 41.26, \"end\": 43.7, \"text\": \"and even grown men.\"}, {\"start\": 43.78, \"end\": 47.32, \"text\": \"Some are typed, others handwritten on notebook paper.\"}, {\"start\": 47.32, \"end\": 52.56, \"text\": \"There are drawings, cards and envelopes filled with pictures of women and even teens in suggestive\"}, {\"start\": 52.56, \"end\": 54.64, \"text\": \"poses.\"}, {\"start\": 54.64, \"end\": 59.36, \"text\": \"Cruz hasn't seen any of the mail because he doesn't have access to it.\"}, {\"start\": 59.36, \"end\": 66.48, \"text\": \"Unless his lawyers or family tell him, he has no way of knowing these letters exists.\"}, {\"start\": 70.08, \"end\": 76.92, \"text\": \"The funeral for Stephon Clark was held today.\"}, {\"start\": 77.08, \"end\": 84.76, \"text\": \"He was the 22-year-old black man killed by Sacramento police.\"}, {\"start\": 84.76, \"end\": 94.32, \"text\": \"The shooting happened 11 days ago but Sacramento officials remain on edge.\"}, {\"start\": 94.32, \"end\": 103.16, \"text\": \"Tensions remain high in the city and authorities are prepared for more protests.\"}, {\"start\": 103.16, \"end\": 108.64, \"text\": \"Protesters are demanding police be held accountable for Clark's death.\"}, {\"start\": 108.64, \"end\": 121.92, \"text\": \"Since the shooting, protesters twice blocked basketball fans from entering Sacramento Kings'\"}, {\"start\": 121.92, \"end\": 125.16, \"text\": \"basketball games.\"}, {\"start\": 125.24, \"end\": 134.0, \"text\": \"And some disrupted a city council meeting earlier this week.\"}, {\"start\": 134.04, \"end\": 137.76, \"text\": \"The state's Attorney General is investigating the fatal shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 137.76, \"end\": 146.6, \"text\": \"Clark's loved ones want an independent autopsy because they don't trust the Sacramento Police\"}, {\"start\": 146.6, \"end\": 152.56, \"text\": \"Department and believe they have been withholding the truth.\"}, {\"start\": 154.36, \"end\": 164.52, \"text\": \"Earlier this week Washington expelled 60 Russian diplomats.\"}, {\"start\": 164.52, \"end\": 181.6, \"text\": \"It was part of a global response to the poisoning of a former Russian double agent and his daughter\"}, {\"start\": 181.6, \"end\": 186.08, \"text\": \"in England.\"}, {\"start\": 186.08, \"end\": 208.96, \"text\": \"UK authorities openly blamed Russia for using a military-grade nerve agent for the poisoning\"}, {\"start\": 208.96, \"end\": 216.64, \"text\": \"on March 4.\"}, {\"start\": 216.64, \"end\": 228.16, \"text\": \"Today Russia retaliated by expelling 60 US diplomats and ordered the closure of the US\"}, {\"start\": 228.16, \"end\": 235.52, \"text\": \"consulate in St. Petersburg.\"}, {\"start\": 235.52, \"end\": 242.72, \"text\": \"Russian officials say the US diplomats have to be out of the country by April 5.\"}, {\"start\": 242.72, \"end\": 253.76, \"text\": \"Russia denies responsibility for the poisoning and President Vladimir Putin has dismissed\"}, {\"start\": 253.76, \"end\": 258.4, \"text\": \"it as \\\"delirium.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 262.72, \"end\": 268.88, \"text\": \"Authorities are looking for this teen.\"}, {\"start\": 268.88, \"end\": 279.12, \"text\": \"Fifteen-year-old Devonte Hart is the teen whose picture went viral in 2014.\"}, {\"start\": 279.84, \"end\": 283.84, \"text\": \"In the picture he's hugging a police officer as tears streamed down his cheek.\"}, {\"start\": 283.84, \"end\": 291.28, \"text\": \"It was taken during a protest in Portland over the police-involved shooting death of\"}, {\"start\": 291.28, \"end\": 293.84, \"text\": \"Michael Brown.\"}, {\"start\": 293.84, \"end\": 298.76, \"text\": \"Now Hart and two of his sisters are missing.\"}, {\"start\": 298.76, \"end\": 307.52, \"text\": \"Hart's parents and three other siblings died after the family's vehicle drove off a cliff\"}, {\"start\": 307.52, \"end\": 310.88, \"text\": \"near Mendocino, California.\"}, {\"start\": 310.88, \"end\": 318.24, \"text\": \"Authorities do not know if Hart and his sisters were with the family or if they might be staying\"}, {\"start\": 318.44, \"end\": 321.04, \"text\": \"with friends.\"}, {\"start\": 321.04, \"end\": 326.76, \"text\": \"The Mendocino Sheriff's department is asking anyone with information to give them a call\"}, {\"start\": 326.8, \"end\": 331.68, \"text\": \"at 707-463-4086.\"}, {\"start\": 334.0, \"end\": 338.27, \"text\": \"Here's a bit of history for you today.\"}, {\"start\": 338.28, \"end\": 347.36, \"text\": \"On this day 45 years ago the last American ground troops left Vietnam.\"}, {\"start\": 347.36, \"end\": 351.4, \"text\": \"The servicemembers boarded a flight on March 29, 1973 after almost 10 years of military\"}, {\"start\": 351.4, \"end\": 353.56, \"text\": \"intervention.\"}, {\"start\": 353.56, \"end\": 365.0, \"text\": \"The final withdrawal came two months after the signing of the Vietnam peace treaty.\"}, {\"start\": 365.08, \"end\": 371.28, \"text\": \"According to the US Department of Defense more than 2 million US troops served in South\"}, {\"start\": 371.44, \"end\": 373.0, \"text\": \"Vietnam.\"}, {\"start\": 373.0, \"end\": 381.24, \"text\": \"58,220 Americans died in the war along with 1 million civilians.\"}, {\"start\": 381.52, \"end\": 387.36, \"text\": \"1,601 American soldiers are still unaccounted for.\"}, {\"start\": 389.68, \"end\": 398.6, \"text\": \"The first case of super-resistant gonorrhea has been reported in the United Kingdom.\"}, {\"start\": 398.6, \"end\": 405.84, \"text\": \"Health officials say a man is infected with a form of gonorrhea that is completely resistant\"}, {\"start\": 405.84, \"end\": 407.52, \"text\": \"to treatment.\"}, {\"start\": 407.52, \"end\": 416.44, \"text\": \"The man caught the sexually transmitted disease in southeast Asia one month before his symptoms\"}, {\"start\": 416.76, \"end\": 418.72, \"text\": \"began.\"}, {\"start\": 418.92, \"end\": 434.2, \"text\": \"Officials say the man is being treated intravenously with the antibiotic Ertapenem.\"}, {\"start\": 434.2, \"end\": 436.84, \"text\": \"It appears to be effective for now.\"}, {\"start\": 436.84, \"end\": 442.24, \"text\": \"The man will be tested again in April.\"}, {\"start\": 444.92, \"end\": 447.24, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 447.24, \"end\": 449.28, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 449.28, \"end\": 452.64, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 452.68, \"end\": 459.6, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 459.6, \"end\": 467.44, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "_xBb_SJ4J_8": {
    "video_id": "_xBb_SJ4J_8",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.30.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171201",
    "duration": 605,
    "view_count": 467,
    "description": "November 30, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-MATT LAUER APOLOGIZES, FACES MORE ALLEGATIONS\n-RUSSELL SIMMONS STEPS DOWN AFTER SEX ASSAULT CLAIM\n-SEMINOLE HEIGHTS SUSPECT IN COURT\n-HEARING FOR 1983 RACIALLY MOTIVATED KILLING\n-GOP TAX PLAN MOVING AHEAD\n-KAEPERNICK WINS MUHAMMAD ALI LEGACY AWARD\n-JIM NABORS DIES\n-APPLE URGING USERS TO INSTALL CRITICAL UPDATE\n-DEER ENROLLS IN MIDDLE SCHOOL\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.86, \"end\": 8.82, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.82, \"end\": 11.38, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.5, \"end\": 12.78, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.8, \"end\": 14.6, \"text\": \"Here are you top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.66, \"end\": 29.24, \"text\": \"Matt Lauer is responding to the sexual harassment accusations that cost him his job at NBC News.\"}, {\"start\": 29.28, \"end\": 37.66, \"text\": \"In a statement, the former \\\"Today\\\" host writes: \\\"There are no words to express my sorrow and\"}, {\"start\": 37.67, \"end\": 41.51, \"text\": \"regret for the pain I caused others by words and actions.\"}, {\"start\": 41.51, \"end\": 46.469, \"text\": \"To the people I've hurt, I'm truly sorry.\"}, {\"start\": 46.469, \"end\": 53.039, \"text\": \"As I am writing this, I realized that the depth of the damage and disappointment I have\"}, {\"start\": 53.04, \"end\": 55.04, \"text\": \"left behind at home and at NBC.\"}, {\"start\": 55.04, \"end\": 61.0, \"text\": \"Some of what is being said about me is untrue or mischaracterized, but there is enough truth\"}, {\"start\": 61.02, \"end\": 65.58, \"text\": \"in these stories to make me feel embarrassed and shame.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 65.64, \"end\": 73.68, \"text\": \"Since yesterday more women have come forward and filed complaints with NBC regarding Lauer.\"}, {\"start\": 73.76, \"end\": 79.58, \"text\": \"Lauer still has about a year left on his contract.\"}, {\"start\": 79.58, \"end\": 83.76, \"text\": \"NBC has not said who will replace him.\"}, {\"start\": 85.3, \"end\": 105.859, \"text\": \"Russell Simmons, the founder of hip-hop music label Def Jam Recordings and CEO of Rush Communications,\"}, {\"start\": 105.86, \"end\": 111.84, \"text\": \"is stepping down from his companies after being accused of sexual assault.\"}, {\"start\": 111.84, \"end\": 122.26, \"text\": \"Screenwriter Jenny Lumet says Simmons forced her to have sex with him in 1991.\"}, {\"start\": 122.3, \"end\": 134.5, \"text\": \"She detailed the encounter in a column published by the Hollywood Reporter on Thursday.\"}, {\"start\": 134.54, \"end\": 141.8, \"text\": \"Simmons released a statement saying: \\\"I know Jenny and her family and have seen her several\"}, {\"start\": 141.8, \"end\": 146.86, \"text\": \"times over the years since the evening she described.\"}, {\"start\": 146.86, \"end\": 153.42, \"text\": \"While her memory of that evening is very different from mine, it is now clear to me that her\"}, {\"start\": 153.42, \"end\": 157.82, \"text\": \"feelings of fear and intimidation are real.\"}, {\"start\": 157.88, \"end\": 164.06, \"text\": \"While I've never been violent, I have been thoughtless and insensitive in some of my\"}, {\"start\": 164.06, \"end\": 172.14, \"text\": \"relationships over many decades and I sincerely and humbly apologize.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 174.16, \"end\": 188.34, \"text\": \"In Tampa today 24-year-old Howell Donaldson III appeared in court via video conference.\"}, {\"start\": 188.38, \"end\": 196.82, \"text\": \"He is charged in the shooting death of four people in the Seminole Heights neighborhood.\"}, {\"start\": 196.86, \"end\": 204.6, \"text\": \"Donaldson wore a smock to prevent him from hurting himself while the judge spoke to him\"}, {\"start\": 204.6, \"end\": 208.42, \"text\": \"through a video link.\"}, {\"start\": 208.46, \"end\": 215.38, \"text\": \"She ordered him to be held without bond until his next hearing.\"}, {\"start\": 215.48, \"end\": 223.74, \"text\": \"Florida's state attorney is considering seeking the death penalty in this case.\"}, {\"start\": 225.2, \"end\": 236.08, \"text\": \"A 34-year-old murder case in Georgia could go before a grand jury as early as next week.\"}, {\"start\": 236.12, \"end\": 256.6, \"text\": \"Frank Gebhardt and William Moore are accused of murdering Timothy Coggins in 1983.\"}, {\"start\": 256.62, \"end\": 269.46, \"text\": \"Coggins was dragged behind a truck and stabbed numerous times in Spalding County.\"}, {\"start\": 269.5, \"end\": 280.94, \"text\": \"The murder case went cold for decades until October when new witnesses came forward.\"}, {\"start\": 280.96, \"end\": 289.38, \"text\": \"Prosecutors say the murder was racially motivated and happened because Coggins was socializing\"}, {\"start\": 289.38, \"end\": 292.58, \"text\": \"with a white female.\"}, {\"start\": 292.58, \"end\": 305.72, \"text\": \"Gebhardt and Moore remain in jail without bond.\"}, {\"start\": 307.54, \"end\": 314.28, \"text\": \"Republicans may be one step closer to getting their tax reform bill passed.\"}, {\"start\": 314.34, \"end\": 320.76, \"text\": \"Senator John McCain now says he's on board.\"}, {\"start\": 320.78, \"end\": 324.44, \"text\": \"Up until this point he's kept his position on the bill under wraps.\"}, {\"start\": 324.44, \"end\": 331.46, \"text\": \"Republicans have 52 members in the Senate and can only afford to lose two votes if they\"}, {\"start\": 331.47, \"end\": 336.35, \"text\": \"want to get this passed.\"}, {\"start\": 336.35, \"end\": 343.97, \"text\": \"But even if it passes, the Senate bill still needs to be reconciled with the House version\"}, {\"start\": 343.97, \"end\": 351.04, \"text\": \"of bill -- which is noticeably different.\"}, {\"start\": 351.04, \"end\": 356.36, \"text\": \"Republican senators hope to have a vote on the plan before the end of the week.\"}, {\"start\": 358.32, \"end\": 370.16, \"text\": \"Colin Kaepernick is this year's winner of the Sports Illustrated\"}, {\"start\": 370.16, \"end\": 376.52, \"text\": \"Muhammed Ali Legacy award.\"}, {\"start\": 376.54, \"end\": 380.78, \"text\": \"The 30-year-old is the youngest winner.\"}, {\"start\": 380.78, \"end\": 393.3, \"text\": \"The former 49ers quarterback started kneeling during the national anthem in 2016 to draw\"}, {\"start\": 393.3, \"end\": 402.92, \"text\": \"attention to police brutality and social justice issues.\"}, {\"start\": 402.96, \"end\": 413.3, \"text\": \"Protests were soon adopted by several players and have continued this season.\"}, {\"start\": 413.36, \"end\": 423.02, \"text\": \"Kaepernick is expected to attend Sports Illustrated's award show on Tuesday in New York where he\"}, {\"start\": 423.02, \"end\": 429.62, \"text\": \"is being honored.\"}, {\"start\": 429.62, \"end\": 435.96, \"text\": \"The award typically goes to sports figures who have used their platform to initiate change\"}, {\"start\": 435.98, \"end\": 438.86, \"text\": \"over a span decades.\"}, {\"start\": 440.48, \"end\": 450.16, \"text\": \"Legendary singer and actor Jim Nabors has died at the age of 87.\"}, {\"start\": 450.18, \"end\": 461.16, \"text\": \"In the 1960s Nabors spent years on the \\\"Andy Griffiths Show\\\" before spinning off his own\"}, {\"start\": 461.17, \"end\": 467.27, \"text\": \"show \\\"Gomer Pyle: USMC.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 467.27, \"end\": 473.02, \"text\": \"Nabor also had an incredible singing voice.\"}, {\"start\": 473.02, \"end\": 476.84, \"text\": \"During his career he recorded more than 12 albums.\"}, {\"start\": 476.9, \"end\": 482.5, \"text\": \"In 2013 at the age of 82 Nabors finally married his best friend and partner of 30 years,\"}, {\"start\": 482.5, \"end\": 486.199, \"text\": \"Stan Cadwallader.\"}, {\"start\": 486.2, \"end\": 501.56, \"text\": \"They wed in Seattle just a month after same-sex marriage became legal in the state.\"}, {\"start\": 501.6, \"end\": 509.1, \"text\": \"Although the actor never publicly announced he was gay, he said he never kept it a secret either.\"}, {\"start\": 511.6, \"end\": 521.96, \"text\": \"Apple is urging customers with Mac High Sierra operating systems to install the latest patch\"}, {\"start\": 521.97, \"end\": 525.04, \"text\": \"as soon as possible.\"}, {\"start\": 525.04, \"end\": 530.86, \"text\": \"Recently the company found out there is a major flaw in the O-S security.\"}, {\"start\": 530.86, \"end\": 536.1, \"text\": \"The flaw would allow anyone to have administrative access to your computer\"}, {\"start\": 536.1, \"end\": 538.54, \"text\": \"without knowing the password.\"}, {\"start\": 538.54, \"end\": 542.02, \"text\": \"Installing the patch will fix the problem.\"}, {\"start\": 542.04, \"end\": 547.86, \"text\": \"Just go to the Mac App Store to download.\"}, {\"start\": 549.2, \"end\": 557.12, \"text\": \"It was a wild day for middle school students in Enterprise, Mississippi.\"}, {\"start\": 557.14, \"end\": 559.5, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 559.54, \"end\": 562.76, \"text\": \"A deer found its way into the school.\"}, {\"start\": 562.78, \"end\": 568.3, \"text\": \"As it tried to escape it slid down the hall right out the front door.\"}, {\"start\": 568.34, \"end\": 574.18, \"text\": \"You can see kids scurrying to get out of the way as animal slides out the door.\"}, {\"start\": 574.24, \"end\": 576.84, \"text\": \"No one was injured in the surreal incident.\"}, {\"start\": 578.74, \"end\": 580.82, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for the day.\"}, {\"start\": 580.88, \"end\": 582.62, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 582.64, \"end\": 585.18, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 585.2, \"end\": 590.4, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 590.42, \"end\": 597.74, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "jdqmM_HiTC4": {
    "video_id": "jdqmM_HiTC4",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.16.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171217",
    "duration": 441,
    "view_count": 469,
    "description": "December 16, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-HOW DOES THE NEW TAX BILL AFFECT YOU?\n-ANITA HILL TO CHAIR HOLLYWOOD ANTI-SEX HARASSMENT PANEL\n-CDC'S LIST OF FORBIDDEN WORDS\n-CRUISE CONTROL DESIGNS COULD SOLVE TRAFFIC JAMS\n-2022 OLYMPIC LOGO REVEALED\n-CAT FROM GEORGIA ENDS UP IN CALIFORNIA\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE Our talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizat",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.72, \"end\": 7.72, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.72, \"end\": 9.8, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.82, \"end\": 11.84, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 11.84, \"end\": 14.42, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.54, \"end\": 22.4, \"text\": \"Yesterday Republicans released the final version of their tax bill, which means they are one\"}, {\"start\": 22.4, \"end\": 29.58, \"text\": \"step closer to fulfilling the promise of passing tax breaks by Christmas.\"}, {\"start\": 29.64, \"end\": 35.74, \"text\": \"But how will the new tax bill affect you -- the taxpayer?\"}, {\"start\": 35.8, \"end\": 44.5, \"text\": \"You will see some benefits like a doubling of the standard deduction --\"}, {\"start\": 44.5, \"end\": 49.38, \"text\": \"although that's scheduled to go away after eight years.\"}, {\"start\": 49.38, \"end\": 54.38, \"text\": \"Your personal income tax rate may also lower by one or two percent\"}, {\"start\": 54.4, \"end\": 58.1, \"text\": \"depending on how much you make.\"}, {\"start\": 58.12, \"end\": 65.8, \"text\": \"If you have kids, that child tax credit doubles to $2,000.\"}, {\"start\": 65.8, \"end\": 71.5, \"text\": \"If that credit is more than what you owe in taxes,\"}, {\"start\": 71.56, \"end\": 74.02, \"text\": \"you get to keep most of that extra money.\"}, {\"start\": 74.02, \"end\": 79.96, \"text\": \"The new bill is scheduled to be presented for a vote on the House floor next week.\"}, {\"start\": 82.44, \"end\": 89.74, \"text\": \"Top Hollywood executives have chosen Anita Hill to chair the newly formed commission\"}, {\"start\": 89.74, \"end\": 95.58, \"text\": \"on sexual harassment and equity in the workplace.\"}, {\"start\": 95.58, \"end\": 104.92, \"text\": \"In 1991 Hill leveled sexual harassment allegations against Clarence Thomas during his Supreme\"}, {\"start\": 104.92, \"end\": 118.52, \"text\": \"Court confirmation hearings.\"}, {\"start\": 118.52, \"end\": 123.6, \"text\": \"She said it happened when the two worked together at the Department of Education.\"}, {\"start\": 123.62, \"end\": 132.4, \"text\": \"Hill says she is proud to lead the new commission and that it's time to end the culture of silence.\"}, {\"start\": 132.44, \"end\": 138.36, \"text\": \"The commission was formed after allegations of sexual abuse by powerful men in the\"}, {\"start\": 138.36, \"end\": 147.94, \"text\": \"entertainment business.\"}, {\"start\": 147.94, \"end\": 166.04, \"text\": \"Those men include Harvey Weinstein, Matt Lauer, Kevin Spacey, Louis CK, Russell Simmons\"}, {\"start\": 166.04, \"end\": 168.92, \"text\": \"and Al Franken.\"}, {\"start\": 171.04, \"end\": 184.4, \"text\": \"According to the Washington Post, policy analysts at the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention\"}, {\"start\": 184.4, \"end\": 191.8, \"text\": \"in Atlanta had a meeting Thursday with senior CDC officials.\"}, {\"start\": 191.8, \"end\": 200.54, \"text\": \"They were reportedly given a list of forbidden words the White House apparently does not\"}, {\"start\": 200.58, \"end\": 206.2, \"text\": \"want to see in the CDC's next budget report.\"}, {\"start\": 206.2, \"end\": 207.42, \"text\": \"Here are a few of those words:\"}, {\"start\": 207.42, \"end\": 225.44, \"text\": \"Fetus, transgender, diversity, vulnerable, entitlement, evidence-based and science-based.\"}, {\"start\": 225.44, \"end\": 231.36, \"text\": \"CNN is reached out to the CDC but did not receive a response.\"}, {\"start\": 233.48, \"end\": 238.6, \"text\": \"MIT researchers believe they have found a new way to stop\"}, {\"start\": 238.6, \"end\": 245.04, \"text\": \"frustrating \\\"stop-and-go\\\" traffic.\"}, {\"start\": 245.16, \"end\": 255.28, \"text\": \"Researchers published a paper this week offering\"}, {\"start\": 255.28, \"end\": 265.72, \"text\": \"cruise control as a solution to help alleviate traffic jams.\"}, {\"start\": 265.72, \"end\": 274.68, \"text\": \"The report proposes redesigning the cruise control feature on cars to factor in the space\"}, {\"start\": 274.8, \"end\": 276.88, \"text\": \"in front and behind the vehicle.\"}, {\"start\": 277.0, \"end\": 284.72, \"text\": \"Simulations showed that keeping the same distance between the vehicle in the front and the vehicle\"}, {\"start\": 284.72, \"end\": 288.56, \"text\": \"in the back prevents traffic jams.\"}, {\"start\": 288.56, \"end\": 290.96, \"text\": \"But there is a catch.\"}, {\"start\": 290.96, \"end\": 295.12, \"text\": \"In order for the redesigned cruise control to work and have an immediate impact on traffic\"}, {\"start\": 295.12, \"end\": 304.6, \"text\": \"lots of drivers have to use the technology.\"}, {\"start\": 307.76, \"end\": 313.08, \"text\": \"There was a big reveal in Beijing Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 313.08, \"end\": 322.12, \"text\": \"The logos for the 2022 Olympics and the Paralympic Winter games were revealed.\"}, {\"start\": 322.12, \"end\": 334.72, \"text\": \"The Olympic emblem is named \\\"Winter Dream\\\" with a wisp of Chinese calligraphy,\"}, {\"start\": 334.72, \"end\": 339.52, \"text\": \"a skater and a skier.\"}, {\"start\": 339.52, \"end\": 347.76, \"text\": \"The emblem for the Paralympics is called \\\"Flying High\\\" -- an abstract image\"}, {\"start\": 347.76, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"of an athlete fighting for victory.\"}, {\"start\": 356.6, \"end\": 368.16, \"text\": \"Five-year-old \\\"Kitty-Bitty\\\" went missing from Pooler, Georgia on the 4th of July.\"}, {\"start\": 368.16, \"end\": 373.92, \"text\": \"He was discovered under a Pepsi truck by a driver in Riverside\"}, {\"start\": 373.92, \"end\": 385.8, \"text\": \"County, California this month.\"}, {\"start\": 385.8, \"end\": 393.04, \"text\": \"The driver called animal services.\"}, {\"start\": 393.16, \"end\": 398.48, \"text\": \"Animal services officials says Kitty-Bitty's owners were ecstatic when they heard the news.\"}, {\"start\": 398.48, \"end\": 403.16, \"text\": \"Officials used Kitty-Bitty's rabies tag to track down his owners.\"}, {\"start\": 403.24, \"end\": 408.52, \"text\": \"He was dehydrated and hungry but is expected to be just fine.\"}, {\"start\": 408.52, \"end\": 413.28, \"text\": \"Officials are now making arrangements to fly the cat back home before Christmas.\"}, {\"start\": 415.8, \"end\": 418.44, \"text\": \"And those your top stories today.\"}, {\"start\": 418.52, \"end\": 419.8, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 419.84, \"end\": 422.44, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 422.56, \"end\": 427.76, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 427.8, \"end\": 435.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "gKWW_jO_CO8": {
    "video_id": "gKWW_jO_CO8",
    "title": "October 7, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171008",
    "duration": 602,
    "view_count": 169,
    "description": "October 7, 2017\nNews for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).\n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-NATE WILL BE CATEGORY 2 STORM\n-FEMA PREPARED FOR NATE\n-BIRTH CONTROL COVERAGE CUT?\n-FREEZER DEATH RULED AN ACCIDENT\n-JOURNALIST'S DECAPITATED HEAD FOUND\n-TRAFFIC DEATHS RISE BUT CARS SAFER\n-JAMES WOODS RETIRES FROM ACTING\n-17-HUNDRED POUND PUMPKIN\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizat",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 10.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.0, \"end\": 15.0, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 15.0, \"end\": 18.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.0, \"end\": 24.0, \"text\": \"Forecasters have been watching Hurricane\"}, {\"start\": 24.0, \"end\": 26.0, \"text\": \"Nate very closely.\"}, {\"start\": 27.0, \"end\": 35.0, \"text\": \"They believe hurricane Nate will make landfall south of New Orleans overnight.\"}, {\"start\": 36.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"Forecasters say Nate will be a Category 2 and will\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 45.0, \"text\": \"affect the Louisiana, Mississippi, Alabama and\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 47.0, \"text\": \"Florida area.\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"The storm could bring strong waves and wind gusts of 100 mph.\"}, {\"start\": 55.0, \"end\": 60.0, \"text\": \"It willl start in Louisiana and move to the Florida panhandle.\"}, {\"start\": 60.0, \"end\": 64.0, \"text\": \"Some areas could be hit with heavy flooding and dangerous\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 67.0, \"text\": \"storm surges.\"}, {\"start\": 67.0, \"end\": 72.0, \"text\": \"At least a million people who live along the Gulf Coast\"}, {\"start\": 74.0, \"end\": 80.0, \"text\": \"could lose power.\"}, {\"start\": 80.0, \"end\": 85.0, \"text\": \"Some areas in New Orleans near the\"}, {\"start\": 86.0, \"end\": 92.0, \"text\": \"coastline are being evacuated.\"}, {\"start\": 92.0, \"end\": 96.0, \"text\": \"For the past six weeks two hurricanes have hit\"}, {\"start\": 96.0, \"end\": 97.0, \"text\": \"the United States -- Hurricane Harvey and\"}, {\"start\": 97.0, \"end\": 104.0, \"text\": \"Hurricane Irma. Now Hurricane Nate will\"}, {\"start\": 104.0, \"end\": 108.0, \"text\": \"make the third hurricane in six weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 111.0, \"end\": 115.0, \"text\": \"This morning President Trump assured the\"}, {\"start\": 115.0, \"end\": 123.0, \"text\": \"people living in the path of the storm\"}, {\"start\": 123.0, \"end\": 128.0, \"text\": \"that the federal government -- in particular FEMA --\"}, {\"start\": 129.0, \"end\": 134.0, \"text\": \"is ready to respond. He went\"}, {\"start\": 134.0, \"end\": 137.0, \"text\": \"on to say everyone living in Louisiana,\"}, {\"start\": 137.0, \"end\": 141.0, \"text\": \"Mississippi, Alabama and Florida -- it is important\"}, {\"start\": 142.0, \"end\": 146.0, \"text\": \"that they obey law enforcement\"}, {\"start\": 148.0, \"end\": 152.0, \"text\": \"and local officials and be safe.\"}, {\"start\": 154.0, \"end\": 157.0, \"text\": \"During the Obama administration\"}, {\"start\": 159.0, \"end\": 163.0, \"text\": \"companies were required to provide free birth control, regardless\"}, {\"start\": 165.0, \"end\": 169.0, \"text\": \"of that company's religious beliefs.\"}, {\"start\": 172.0, \"end\": 177.0, \"text\": \"Now President Trump wants to change that\"}, {\"start\": 178.0, \"end\": 181.0, \"text\": \"with the new rule:  If company's\"}, {\"start\": 181.0, \"end\": 185.0, \"text\": \"religious beliefs go against birth control, they are not required to\"}, {\"start\": 185.0, \"end\": 188.0, \"text\": \"provide free insurance for birth control.\"}, {\"start\": 188.0, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"Some people support the new rule and say it's an advancement for religious freedoms.\"}, {\"start\": 197.0, \"end\": 201.0, \"text\": \"Other groups are worried  this is a step backwards\"}, {\"start\": 202.0, \"end\": 207.0, \"text\": \"for women's health rights. The new rule\"}, {\"start\": 207.0, \"end\": 212.0, \"text\": \"is being heavily debated and will\"}, {\"start\": 213.0, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"probably be taken to a higher court. Some groups who are very\"}, {\"start\": 217.0, \"end\": 225.0, \"text\": \"upset with the new rule and plan on filing lawsuits.\"}, {\"start\": 228.0, \"end\": 233.0, \"text\": \"Remember a month ago we showed you this video.\"}, {\"start\": 233.0, \"end\": 238.0, \"text\": \"It's from the Crowne Plaza Hotel in Chicago.\"}, {\"start\": 238.0, \"end\": 242.0, \"text\": \"The woman in the video is Kenneka Jenkins\"}, {\"start\": 247.0, \"end\": 252.0, \"text\": \"She is seen walking  unsteady in the hallways\"}, {\"start\": 252.0, \"end\": 257.0, \"text\": \"and in the kitchen area. The next morning\"}, {\"start\": 257.0, \"end\": 265.0, \"text\": \"she was found dead in a walk-in freezer in the kitchen.\"}, {\"start\": 265.0, \"end\": 273.0, \"text\": \"Today the Cook County coroner\"}, {\"start\": 274.0, \"end\": 282.0, \"text\": \"said that the woman died of hypothermia.\"}, {\"start\": 282.0, \"end\": 286.0, \"text\": \"her death was ruled an accident.\"}, {\"start\": 286.0, \"end\": 290.0, \"text\": \"The coroner also says alcohol intoxication and a\"}, {\"start\": 290.1, \"end\": 294.1, \"text\": \"drug used for migraines factored into her death.\"}, {\"start\": 294.1, \"end\": 302.1, \"text\": \"Jenkins' family has filed a lawsuit\"}, {\"start\": 305.0, \"end\": 313.0, \"text\": \"In Sweden, police say they have found missing\"}, {\"start\": 313.0, \"end\": 315.0, \"text\": \"journalist Kim Wall.\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 321.0, \"text\": \"Police say she was found in bags. Her\"}, {\"start\": 321.0, \"end\": 328.0, \"text\": \"body cut up into pieces including her head.\"}, {\"start\": 328.0, \"end\": 332.0, \"text\": \"They also found a knife in the bag.\"}, {\"start\": 334.0, \"end\": 339.0, \"text\": \"Wall had been missing for about two months. She was\"}, {\"start\": 340.0, \"end\": 348.0, \"text\": \"last seen getting on a private submarine\"}, {\"start\": 349.0, \"end\": 355.0, \"text\": \"owned by investor Peter Madsen.\"}, {\"start\": 355.0, \"end\": 360.0, \"text\": \"That was the last time she was seen. Police say Madsen\"}, {\"start\": 360.0, \"end\": 367.0, \"text\": \"killed Wall but denies the accusation.\"}, {\"start\": 367.0, \"end\": 372.0, \"text\": \"He said Wall's death was an accident.\"}, {\"start\": 374.0, \"end\": 381.0, \"text\": \"When you're driving be careful. According to the National\"}, {\"start\": 382.4, \"end\": 390.4, \"text\": \"Highway Traffic Safety Administration\"}, {\"start\": 396.1, \"end\": 402.1, \"text\": \"cars are becoming safer\"}, {\"start\": 403.0, \"end\": 408.0, \"text\": \"but American roads are deadlier. The NHTSA says in\"}, {\"start\": 408.0, \"end\": 416.0, \"text\": \"2016 the number of traffic fatalities rose nearly 6%.\"}, {\"start\": 418.0, \"end\": 423.0, \"text\": \"Part of the problem is a growing economy.\"}, {\"start\": 424.0, \"end\": 427.0, \"text\": \"A decrease in gas prices\"}, {\"start\": 427.0, \"end\": 435.0, \"text\": \"and an increase in job opportunities means more people are going to work\"}, {\"start\": 436.0, \"end\": 439.0, \"text\": \"and more people are on the roads.\"}, {\"start\": 442.0, \"end\": 450.0, \"text\": \"Yestereday 70-year old actor James Woods announced\"}, {\"start\": 450.0, \"end\": 455.0, \"text\": \"that he is retiring from acting.\"}, {\"start\": 455.0, \"end\": 461.0, \"text\": \"Recently Woods lost his mom and his brother.\"}, {\"start\": 462.0, \"end\": 467.0, \"text\": \"He said he wanted to change his life,\"}, {\"start\": 467.0, \"end\": 472.0, \"text\": \"to not focus on movies anymore. Instead focus on on his love for\"}, {\"start\": 472.0, \"end\": 478.0, \"text\": \"photography, antiques\"}, {\"start\": 478.0, \"end\": 482.0, \"text\": \"and playing poker.\"}, {\"start\": 484.0, \"end\": 490.0, \"text\": \"Woods is an Oscar nominee\"}, {\"start\": 491.0, \"end\": 499.0, \"text\": \"known for his roles in Casino, Salvador\"}, {\"start\": 499.0, \"end\": 507.0, \"text\": \"and Ghost of Mississippi.\"}, {\"start\": 511.0, \"end\": 517.0, \"text\": \"Take a look at this massive pumpkin.\"}, {\"start\": 519.0, \"end\": 527.0, \"text\": \"A Wisconsin family grew it.\"}, {\"start\": 527.0, \"end\": 532.0, \"text\": \"They say they want to win a pumpkin competition this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 532.0, \"end\": 538.0, \"text\": \"And they just might do it.\"}, {\"start\": 539.0, \"end\": 544.0, \"text\": \"The pumpkin is about 6-feet long and\"}, {\"start\": 544.0, \"end\": 547.0, \"text\": \"weighs between 17-hundred and 18-hundred pounds!\"}, {\"start\": 551.0, \"end\": 554.0, \"text\": \"So how did they grow a pumpkin that big?\"}, {\"start\": 558.0, \"end\": 561.0, \"text\": \"The farmer says all he used was organic soil,\"}, {\"start\": 561.1, \"end\": 569.1, \"text\": \"fish oil and kelp.\"}, {\"start\": 573.0, \"end\": 577.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 577.2, \"end\": 581.2, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau. Thank you for watching. Sign 1News.\"}, {\"start\": 581.2, \"end\": 586.2, \"text\": \"And remember to \\\"Like\\\" us on Facebook.\"}, {\"start\": 586.2, \"end\": 594.2, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "N5hHUGVN1G4": {
    "video_id": "N5hHUGVN1G4",
    "title": "NFL player pulls Jeep to strength train (ASL - 3.11.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180312",
    "duration": 62,
    "view_count": 176,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.04, \"end\": 15.14, \"text\": \"New Orleans Saints running back Alvin Kamara has one insane workout.\"}, {\"start\": 15.14, \"end\": 18.98, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 18.98, \"end\": 29.72, \"text\": \"Instead of doing squats to strengthen his legs, he pulls a Jeep!\"}, {\"start\": 29.72, \"end\": 38.7, \"text\": \"And he's holding up a weight rack with four plates on his shoulders.\"}, {\"start\": 38.7, \"end\": 46.08, \"text\": \"He walks about 20 yards and that's believed to burn 90,000 calories.\"}, {\"start\": 46.08, \"end\": 51.98, \"text\": \"It's insane but apparently it's working.\"}, {\"start\": 51.98, \"end\": 61.04, \"text\": \"Kamara was named the NFL's 2018 Offensive Rookie of the Year.\"}]"
  },
  "-NWZsLFjA7A": {
    "video_id": "-NWZsLFjA7A",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.20.19 - News for the Deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20190221",
    "duration": 542,
    "view_count": 2835,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Mueller report could released as early as next week\n-Trump denies New York Times report he tried to interfere with probe\n-Nick Sandmann files lawsuit against Washington Post\n-Another winter mix will hit more than 90 million Americans",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 25.08, \"end\": 27.2, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 27.2, \"end\": 29.5, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 29.5, \"end\": 30.64, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 30.64, \"end\": 33.48, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 38.66, \"end\": 47.54, \"text\": \"Robert Mueller's Russia investigation may still be coming to a close.\"}, {\"start\": 47.54, \"end\": 59.72, \"text\": \"According to people familiar with the matter, Attorney General Bill Barr could announce\"}, {\"start\": 59.72, \"end\": 65.0, \"text\": \"the completion of the Russia probe as early as next week.\"}, {\"start\": 65.0, \"end\": 69.6, \"text\": \"The almost 2-year long investigation will close\"}, {\"start\": 69.6, \"end\": 78.84, \"text\": \"with a confidential report submitted directly to Barr.\"}, {\"start\": 78.84, \"end\": 92.98, \"text\": \"The Attorney General then has to decide how much of that report to share with Congress.\"}, {\"start\": 92.98, \"end\": 104.16, \"text\": \"Legally he doesn't have to disclose any of it.\"}, {\"start\": 104.16, \"end\": 115.48, \"text\": \"However Barr says he plans to be as transparent as possible.\"}, {\"start\": 115.48, \"end\": 122.74, \"text\": \"At the same time officials are mindful about not interfering with White House diplomatic\"}, {\"start\": 122.74, \"end\": 128.02, \"text\": \"efforts that could impact timing as President Trump is planning to travel overseas soon\"}, {\"start\": 128.02, \"end\": 145.02, \"text\": \"for a summit with North Korean leader Kim Jong Un.\"}, {\"start\": 149.64, \"end\": 162.66, \"text\": \"A stunning report in the New York Times claims President Trump asked former Attorney General\"}, {\"start\": 162.66, \"end\": 174.48, \"text\": \"Matt Whitaker to put someone who has supported Trump in charge of investigating hush payments\"}, {\"start\": 174.48, \"end\": 184.8, \"text\": \"made by his former lawyer Michael Cohen.\"}, {\"start\": 184.8, \"end\": 193.78, \"text\": \"It's an allegation the President is denying and one that could put Whitaker in hot water\"}, {\"start\": 193.78, \"end\": 199.6, \"text\": \"in Congress.\"}, {\"start\": 199.6, \"end\": 209.12, \"text\": \"According to the Times, it's unclear how Whitaker responded and there's no evidence he took\"}, {\"start\": 209.12, \"end\": 214.82, \"text\": \"steps to intervene.\"}, {\"start\": 214.82, \"end\": 229.34, \"text\": \"The Times added that Trump soured on Whitaker after his inability to make the change and\"}, {\"start\": 229.34, \"end\": 238.0, \"text\": \"he has since been replaced by Bill Barr.\"}, {\"start\": 238.0, \"end\": 247.56, \"text\": \"But Whitaker could be facing bigger problems.\"}, {\"start\": 247.56, \"end\": 258.84, \"text\": \"He recently told a Congressional committee under oath that the President had never pressured\"}, {\"start\": 258.84, \"end\": 264.72, \"text\": \"him regarding any investigations.\"}, {\"start\": 264.72, \"end\": 280.06, \"text\": \"Whitaker is now under scrutiny by House Democrats for potential perjury.\"}, {\"start\": 280.06, \"end\": 289.16, \"text\": \"Today a Department of Justice spokesperson says Whitaker stands by his testimony and\"}, {\"start\": 289.16, \"end\": 292.0, \"text\": \"Trump is standing by him.\"}, {\"start\": 299.92, \"end\": 310.92, \"text\": \"Nick Sandmann, the Kentucky high school student at the center of a controversial viral video,\"}, {\"start\": 310.92, \"end\": 316.62, \"text\": \"has filed a lawsuit against the Washington Post.\"}, {\"start\": 316.62, \"end\": 342.22, \"text\": \"Sandmann was captured on video smiling as Omaha tribe elder Nathan Phillips played a\"}, {\"start\": 342.22, \"end\": 347.72, \"text\": \"drum and chanted during the annual March for Life rally in Washington, DC last month.\"}, {\"start\": 347.72, \"end\": 360.06, \"text\": \"After the images went viral on social media, Sandmann was accused of bigotry.\"}, {\"start\": 360.08, \"end\": 370.84, \"text\": \"According to the lawsuit, the Post wrongfully targeted and bullied\"}, {\"start\": 370.84, \"end\": 381.04, \"text\": \"Nicholas because he was the white Catholic student wearing a red \\\"Make America Great\"}, {\"start\": 381.04, \"end\": 384.56, \"text\": \"Again\\\" souvenir cap.\"}, {\"start\": 384.56, \"end\": 393.32, \"text\": \"The suit is seeking $250 million in damages.\"}, {\"start\": 396.96, \"end\": 416.24, \"text\": \"A spokeswoman for the Post said the paper is reviewing the matter and will mount a vigorous defense.\"}, {\"start\": 416.24, \"end\": 423.6, \"text\": \"Another wintry blast is blanketing much of the US.\"}, {\"start\": 423.6, \"end\": 432.88, \"text\": \"Tens of millions of Americans from the Plains to the Northeast are under a winter weather\"}, {\"start\": 432.88, \"end\": 435.24, \"text\": \"watch, warning or advisory.\"}, {\"start\": 435.24, \"end\": 449.7, \"text\": \"Warm, moist air from the Gulf of Mexico is combining with the cool system from the Rockies,\"}, {\"start\": 449.7, \"end\": 452.84, \"text\": \"producing a wintry mix.\"}, {\"start\": 452.84, \"end\": 463.58, \"text\": \"Among the areas expected to get hit especially hard: Washington DC and Baltimore, where up\"}, {\"start\": 463.58, \"end\": 471.54, \"text\": \"to 6 inches of snow and sleet is expected to fall.\"}, {\"start\": 471.54, \"end\": 479.82, \"text\": \"Other parts of the East Coast are also going to get pounded.\"}, {\"start\": 479.82, \"end\": 490.72, \"text\": \"A state of emergency is declared for Wednesday for all of New Jersey's 21 counties.\"}, {\"start\": 490.72, \"end\": 498.12, \"text\": \"And some of the spots not getting snow are getting buckets of rain.\"}, {\"start\": 498.12, \"end\": 509.24, \"text\": \"Flash flood watches are in effect from North Alabama all the way to West Virginia.\"}, {\"start\": 513.74, \"end\": 517.1, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 517.1, \"end\": 518.34, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 518.34, \"end\": 521.44, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 521.44, \"end\": 526.7, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 526.7, \"end\": 528.64, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 528.64, \"end\": 529.74, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 529.74, \"end\": 532.68, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-tAf0xFNJDI": {
    "video_id": "-tAf0xFNJDI",
    "title": "Sign1News 5.23.19 - News for the Deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20190524",
    "duration": 535,
    "view_count": 1601,
    "description": "TODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Congrats Southwest College for the Deaf!\n-Missouri Capitol takes direct hit from tornado\n-Dogs recovering after stolen RV chase\n-Poor diets causing cancer\n-Dolphin found with hose in its body\n-Wanted man will turn himself in for 15K FB 'Likes'\n-Nurse graduates from NYU after working as janitor\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 24.44, \"end\": 25.8, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 25.8, \"end\": 27.2, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 27.2, \"end\": 28.72, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 28.72, \"end\": 31.36, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 34.48, \"end\": 43.6, \"text\": \"We want to send a big congratulations to South West Collegiate Institute for the Deaf in\"}, {\"start\": 43.6, \"end\": 45.2, \"text\": \"Big Springs, Texas.\"}, {\"start\": 45.2, \"end\": 53.56, \"text\": \"Starting in September of this year, the two-year liberal arts school will go by the name South\"}, {\"start\": 53.56, \"end\": 57.88, \"text\": \"West College for the Deaf.\"}, {\"start\": 57.88, \"end\": 68.12, \"text\": \"The school's Board of Trustees met on Monday and announced the name change had passed the\"}, {\"start\": 68.12, \"end\": 72.28, \"text\": \"Texas legislature and has been signed into law.\"}, {\"start\": 72.28, \"end\": 79.08, \"text\": \"School officials say people can start using the new name now but it will take a little\"}, {\"start\": 79.08, \"end\": 87.24, \"text\": \"longer to change signage, stationery and other written forms.\"}, {\"start\": 87.24, \"end\": 93.96, \"text\": \"Again congratulations South West College for the Deaf.\"}, {\"start\": 93.96, \"end\": 103.88, \"text\": \"And a big thank you to Sign1News viewer Dominick Bonura for passing the exciting news on to us.\"}, {\"start\": 110.24, \"end\": 115.04, \"text\": \"A tornado that hit Jefferson City, Missouri\"}, {\"start\": 115.04, \"end\": 121.24, \"text\": \"overnight left at least nine people hurt.\"}, {\"start\": 121.24, \"end\": 128.72, \"text\": \"The twister hit shortly before midnight Wednesday and sent debris swirling more than 2 miles\"}, {\"start\": 128.72, \"end\": 131.6, \"text\": \"into the air.\"}, {\"start\": 131.6, \"end\": 137.64, \"text\": \"The tornado in the state's capitol was part of a storm system that has ravaged the central\"}, {\"start\": 137.64, \"end\": 139.58, \"text\": \"US over the past several days.\"}, {\"start\": 139.58, \"end\": 150.72, \"text\": \"At least 29 tornadoes were reported in the region within a 24 hour period.\"}, {\"start\": 150.72, \"end\": 161.12, \"text\": \"One tornado that hit Golden City, Missouri, which is about 150 miles away from Jefferson\"}, {\"start\": 161.12, \"end\": 163.72, \"text\": \"City, killed three people.\"}, {\"start\": 163.72, \"end\": 174.8, \"text\": \"Rainfall in Tulsa, Oklahoma is threatening the nearby dam that could force residents\"}, {\"start\": 174.8, \"end\": 177.64, \"text\": \"of that city to evacuate quickly if it fails.\"}, {\"start\": 177.64, \"end\": 185.08, \"text\": \"As the storm system continues to move east, parts of Texas, Kansas, Ohio and Pennsylvania\"}, {\"start\": 185.08, \"end\": 189.04, \"text\": \"could see similar severe weather.\"}, {\"start\": 189.16, \"end\": 196.84, \"text\": \"The storm has produced more than 170 tornadoes since Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 201.5, \"end\": 208.84, \"text\": \"Last night television news crews watched as\"}, {\"start\": 208.84, \"end\": 215.46, \"text\": \"an alleged stolen RV led police on a wild and destructive high-speed chase in California.\"}, {\"start\": 215.46, \"end\": 221.12, \"text\": \"A 52 year old woman was behind the wheel and two terrified dogs were on board.\"}, {\"start\": 221.12, \"end\": 227.52, \"text\": \"One dog was so terrified, he jumped out of the broken front windshield while the RV was\"}, {\"start\": 227.52, \"end\": 230.86, \"text\": \"still speeding down the street.\"}, {\"start\": 230.86, \"end\": 236.24, \"text\": \"The vehicle sustained heavy damage as it smashed into anything in its way.\"}, {\"start\": 236.24, \"end\": 241.32, \"text\": \"The chase finally ended when the RV smashed into a tree.\"}, {\"start\": 241.32, \"end\": 247.24, \"text\": \"The suspect jumped out and ran as the second dog chased after her, then was later seen\"}, {\"start\": 247.24, \"end\": 251.76, \"text\": \"posing and panting behind the cuffed suspect.\"}, {\"start\": 251.76, \"end\": 258.72, \"text\": \"The dog that fell onto the highway is alive with a few lacerations and soft tissue damage.\"}, {\"start\": 258.72, \"end\": 262.04, \"text\": \"Both dogs are now in the care of animal control.\"}, {\"start\": 265.68, \"end\": 271.12, \"text\": \"A new study is suggesting tens of thousands\"}, {\"start\": 271.12, \"end\": 276.52, \"text\": \"of Americans get cancer because they don't eat right.\"}, {\"start\": 276.52, \"end\": 285.64, \"text\": \"It says poor diet caused an estimated 80,000 new cancer cases in 2015.\"}, {\"start\": 285.64, \"end\": 297.32, \"text\": \"Researchers say cancer risks have been associated with not eating enough whole grains and dairy\"}, {\"start\": 297.32, \"end\": 303.28, \"text\": \"products as well as eating too much processed meat and red meat in general.\"}, {\"start\": 303.28, \"end\": 312.04, \"text\": \"Colon and rectal cancers are the most common linked to poor diet.\"}, {\"start\": 312.04, \"end\": 320.64, \"text\": \"African-Americans and Latinos, along with men who are 45 to 65 years old are the most likely\"}, {\"start\": 320.64, \"end\": 323.08, \"text\": \"to be affected.\"}, {\"start\": 323.08, \"end\": 331.48, \"text\": \"The study was published in the journal \\\"JNCI Cancer Spectrum\\\" on Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 336.04, \"end\": 343.36, \"text\": \"Florida's fish and wildlife conservation commission\"}, {\"start\": 343.36, \"end\": 354.24, \"text\": \"says the body of a 7 foot male bottlenose dolphin washed ashore on Fort Myers Beach\"}, {\"start\": 354.24, \"end\": 358.72, \"text\": \"in Big Carlos Pass earlier this month.\"}, {\"start\": 358.72, \"end\": 370.08, \"text\": \"Biologists say they found a 24 inch hose lodged in its esophagus and stomach.\"}, {\"start\": 370.08, \"end\": 375.88, \"text\": \"They do not know if swallowing the plastic hose ended up killing the dolphin.\"}, {\"start\": 375.88, \"end\": 381.279, \"text\": \"But biologists note this is a second time in a month that a stranded dolphin from this\"}, {\"start\": 381.28, \"end\": 384.96, \"text\": \"region has ingested plastic.\"}, {\"start\": 390.6, \"end\": 396.6, \"text\": \"A wanted crime suspect in Connecticut apparently\"}, {\"start\": 396.6, \"end\": 399.0, \"text\": \"wants some love.\"}, {\"start\": 399.0, \"end\": 410.12, \"text\": \"Jose Simms is on the loose and police in Torrington have been trying to negotiate his surrender.\"}, {\"start\": 410.12, \"end\": 423.12, \"text\": \"Police now say he agreed to turn himself in if his wanted picture gets 15,000 'likes'\"}, {\"start\": 423.12, \"end\": 427.2, \"text\": \"on the department's Facebook page.\"}, {\"start\": 427.2, \"end\": 433.28, \"text\": \"He is wanted on seven warrants for not appearing in court.\"}, {\"start\": 433.28, \"end\": 441.64, \"text\": \"However police still want anyone who may know where Simms is to call them, in which case,\"}, {\"start\": 441.64, \"end\": 449.32, \"text\": \"they won't wait for Facebook likes.\"}, {\"start\": 454.36, \"end\": 459.6, \"text\": \"Frank Baez came to the United States from\"}, {\"start\": 459.6, \"end\": 464.16, \"text\": \"the Dominican Republic in 2004.\"}, {\"start\": 464.16, \"end\": 468.04, \"text\": \"He was just 15 years old and barely spoke English.\"}, {\"start\": 468.04, \"end\": 472.8, \"text\": \"When he was 17, he got a weekend job as a hospital janitor at New York University's\"}, {\"start\": 472.8, \"end\": 477.8, \"text\": \"medical school.\"}, {\"start\": 477.8, \"end\": 485.12, \"text\": \"He said he loved the fast-paced hospital environment and later took a job as a patient transporter.\"}, {\"start\": 485.12, \"end\": 489.68, \"text\": \"The nurses really like the fact that Baez will constantly ask them about their job and\"}, {\"start\": 489.68, \"end\": 494.44, \"text\": \"it inspired him to take nursing classes at NYU.\"}, {\"start\": 494.44, \"end\": 499.24, \"text\": \"On Monday Baez got his nursing degree from there.\"}, {\"start\": 499.24, \"end\": 505.68, \"text\": \"Now Baez says he's getting ready to take his licensing boards and hopes to get a nursing\"}, {\"start\": 505.68, \"end\": 508.72, \"text\": \"job at NYU.\"}, {\"start\": 512.2, \"end\": 513.96, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 513.96, \"end\": 514.88, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 514.88, \"end\": 516.68, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 516.68, \"end\": 520.12, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 520.12, \"end\": 521.24, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 521.24, \"end\": 522.44, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 522.44, \"end\": 524.8, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-QHnZBBE8Ho": {
    "video_id": "-QHnZBBE8Ho",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.7.19 - News for the Deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20190308",
    "duration": 592,
    "view_count": 677,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Severe weather possibly headed towards Alabama again\n-Alex Trebek announces he has stage 4 cancer\n-Murdered dentist found in suitcase\n-Senator reveals her sexual assault in the military\n-Mark Zuckerberg wants more private Facebook\n-FDA approves new drug for depression\n-20 states have proposed anti-vaccination legislation",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 25.54, \"end\": 26.84, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 26.84, \"end\": 29.2, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 29.2, \"end\": 30.7, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 30.7, \"end\": 32.94, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 38.7, \"end\": 50.26, \"text\": \"Residents in Lee County, Alabama are still trying to recover from the deadly EF-4 tornado\"}, {\"start\": 50.26, \"end\": 52.54, \"text\": \"that killed 23 people last weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 52.54, \"end\": 59.26, \"text\": \"Now the National Weather Service says another severe storm could be headed towards Alabama\"}, {\"start\": 59.26, \"end\": 60.66, \"text\": \"this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 60.66, \"end\": 68.3, \"text\": \"Meteorologists say the storm will most likely bring more damaging winds, hail and heavy\"}, {\"start\": 68.3, \"end\": 73.1, \"text\": \"rain and the possibility of more tornadoes can't be ruled out either.\"}, {\"start\": 73.1, \"end\": 84.38, \"text\": \"Officials say the severe storm risk is for nearly all of Alabama on Saturday and parts\"}, {\"start\": 84.38, \"end\": 86.76, \"text\": \"of the state on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 86.76, \"end\": 91.82, \"text\": \"Residents are being urged to stay alert and be prepared.\"}, {\"start\": 93.82, \"end\": 105.44, \"text\": \"Long time Jeopardy host Alex Trebek announced Wednesday that he has been diagnosed with\"}, {\"start\": 105.44, \"end\": 108.86, \"text\": \"Stage 4 pancreatic cancer.\"}, {\"start\": 108.86, \"end\": 114.64, \"text\": \"Trebek says he is aware the prognosis for Stage 4 pancreatic cancer is not good.\"}, {\"start\": 114.64, \"end\": 122.44, \"text\": \"According to the American Cancer Society, pancreatic cancer has a five-year survival\"}, {\"start\": 122.44, \"end\": 125.96, \"text\": \"rate of just 9 percent.\"}, {\"start\": 125.96, \"end\": 132.4, \"text\": \"But Trebek promised to fight and said he plans on beating the low survival rate for the disease.\"}, {\"start\": 132.4, \"end\": 139.12, \"text\": \"The 78-year-old also joked that he has to beat the disease because under the terms of\"}, {\"start\": 139.12, \"end\": 145.08, \"text\": \"his contract he has to host the show for three more years.\"}, {\"start\": 150.12, \"end\": 164.24, \"text\": \"Authorities in Australia say the body of 32-year-old Preethi Reddy was found stuffed inside a suitcase\"}, {\"start\": 164.24, \"end\": 165.88, \"text\": \"in her own car.\"}, {\"start\": 165.88, \"end\": 169.28, \"text\": \"She had been stabbed several times.\"}, {\"start\": 169.28, \"end\": 174.72, \"text\": \"Investigators suspect her killer was her former boyfriend, who she had run into at a dentist's\"}, {\"start\": 174.72, \"end\": 176.72, \"text\": \"conference.\"}, {\"start\": 176.72, \"end\": 182.98, \"text\": \"But he died suspiciously in a fiery car accident the day after Reddy's body was found.\"}, {\"start\": 182.98, \"end\": 194.92, \"text\": \"Authorities say he deliberately slammed his car into a semi trailer just hours after he\"}, {\"start\": 194.92, \"end\": 198.58, \"text\": \"had spoken to detectives about Reddy's missing persons report.\"}, {\"start\": 198.58, \"end\": 204.64, \"text\": \"Now Reddy's family and police are wondering what led to this tragedy.\"}, {\"start\": 204.64, \"end\": 208.98, \"text\": \"Investigators are trying to figure out why Reddy met with her ex-boyfriend following\"}, {\"start\": 208.98, \"end\": 212.52, \"text\": \"the conference, what happened in the hours after she last contacted her family and where\"}, {\"start\": 212.52, \"end\": 215.86, \"text\": \"exactly she was attacked.\"}, {\"start\": 220.88, \"end\": 231.84, \"text\": \"There was powerful testimony on Capitol Hill yesterday as freshman senator Martha McSally\"}, {\"start\": 231.84, \"end\": 235.88, \"text\": \"revealed she was raped by a superior officer while serving in the military.\"}, {\"start\": 235.88, \"end\": 242.32, \"text\": \"McSally shared her own experience during a hearing of sexual assault in the military.\"}, {\"start\": 242.32, \"end\": 247.16, \"text\": \"McSally was the first American woman to fly in combat.\"}, {\"start\": 247.16, \"end\": 255.98, \"text\": \"During her career with the Air Force, she rose to the rank of colonel before retiring.\"}, {\"start\": 255.98, \"end\": 264.82, \"text\": \"But she almost left the Air Force earlier because of her assault.\"}, {\"start\": 264.82, \"end\": 274.68, \"text\": \"According to the Department of Defense, in 2017 the military received nearly 7,000 reports\"}, {\"start\": 274.68, \"end\": 277.78, \"text\": \"of sexual assaults involving servicemembers.\"}, {\"start\": 277.78, \"end\": 286.0, \"text\": \"And a recent Smithsonian poll found that about two thirds of current and former female\"}, {\"start\": 286.0, \"end\": 291.0, \"text\": \"servicemembers experienced sexual harassment or assault.\"}, {\"start\": 291.0, \"end\": 298.4, \"text\": \"Within the past decade the Department of Defense has dedicated more resources to preventing\"}, {\"start\": 298.4, \"end\": 304.8, \"text\": \"unwanted sexual conduct, supporting survivors and prosecuting sexual offenders.\"}, {\"start\": 304.8, \"end\": 309.26, \"text\": \"But lawmakers agree more work needs to be done.\"}, {\"start\": 312.94, \"end\": 324.3, \"text\": \"Facebook founder and CEO Mark Zuckerberg says he wants to reposition Facebook as a privacy-focused\"}, {\"start\": 324.3, \"end\": 326.1, \"text\": \"platform.\"}, {\"start\": 326.1, \"end\": 334.48, \"text\": \"He wants to integrate all the messaging services Facebook owns and encrypt messages on them.\"}, {\"start\": 334.48, \"end\": 342.86, \"text\": \"That includes WhatsApp, Instagram direct and Facebook messenger.\"}, {\"start\": 342.86, \"end\": 351.68, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg also says he wants to give users more control over how long their content lives online.\"}, {\"start\": 351.68, \"end\": 356.88, \"text\": \"That would involve letting them choose for it to be automatically deleted after a set\"}, {\"start\": 356.88, \"end\": 364.62, \"text\": \"amount of time, like on Snapchat and Instagram stories.\"}, {\"start\": 364.62, \"end\": 372.26, \"text\": \"According to Zuckerberg, users of Facebook's various platforms will be able to keep their\"}, {\"start\": 372.26, \"end\": 376.88, \"text\": \"accounts separate after the services are integrated if they wish.\"}, {\"start\": 376.88, \"end\": 385.64, \"text\": \"However some lawmakers worry integrating services would give Facebook too much visibility into\"}, {\"start\": 385.64, \"end\": 389.56, \"text\": \"user privacy information and online habits.\"}, {\"start\": 393.52, \"end\": 398.28, \"text\": \"Millions of people suffer from depression.\"}, {\"start\": 398.28, \"end\": 404.4, \"text\": \"But approximately one third of those that suffer from major depression are considered\"}, {\"start\": 404.4, \"end\": 407.82, \"text\": \"treatment-resistant, meaning nothing works.\"}, {\"start\": 407.82, \"end\": 412.699, \"text\": \"Well help and hope maybe on the way.\"}, {\"start\": 412.699, \"end\": 420.97, \"text\": \"The US Food and Drug Administration just approved the second-ever drug, and first one in a decade,\"}, {\"start\": 420.97, \"end\": 427.02, \"text\": \"to treat those with treatment-resistant depression.\"}, {\"start\": 427.02, \"end\": 438.98, \"text\": \"The drug is Spravato and it contains esketamine, the chemical cousin of ketamine, a powerful\"}, {\"start\": 438.98, \"end\": 446.96, \"text\": \"anesthetic which is used illegally as club drug Special K.\"}, {\"start\": 446.96, \"end\": 451.24, \"text\": \"It's administered as a nasal spray and is fast acting.\"}, {\"start\": 451.24, \"end\": 458.56, \"text\": \"Patients say that is a welcome change since other treatments like Prozac can take weeks\"}, {\"start\": 458.56, \"end\": 461.1, \"text\": \"or months to work.\"}, {\"start\": 461.1, \"end\": 468.9, \"text\": \"There are side effects including dizziness, lethargy and feeling drunk and temporarily\"}, {\"start\": 468.9, \"end\": 471.7, \"text\": \"disconnected from your body and mind.\"}, {\"start\": 471.7, \"end\": 479.06, \"text\": \"Because of its potency and potential for abuse, the drug will not be sent home with patients.\"}, {\"start\": 479.06, \"end\": 485.7, \"text\": \"It will be administered at the doctor's office and patients will be monitored for at least\"}, {\"start\": 485.7, \"end\": 486.84, \"text\": \"two hours afterwards.\"}, {\"start\": 490.98, \"end\": 497.78, \"text\": \"According to the World Health Organization, vaccination is one of the most cost-effective\"}, {\"start\": 497.78, \"end\": 504.1, \"text\": \"ways to avoid diseases and it prevents 2 to 3 million deaths every year.\"}, {\"start\": 504.11, \"end\": 509.599, \"text\": \"And yet more and more states are introducing bills that could make it easier for people\"}, {\"start\": 509.599, \"end\": 513.479, \"text\": \"to opt out of vaccinations.\"}, {\"start\": 513.48, \"end\": 523.26, \"text\": \"According to the American Academy of Pediatrics, at least 20 states have introduced bills that\"}, {\"start\": 523.26, \"end\": 529.46, \"text\": \"would broaden the reason why parents can exempt their children from getting vaccines and require\"}, {\"start\": 529.46, \"end\": 534.36, \"text\": \"doctors to provide more information on the risks of vaccines.\"}, {\"start\": 534.36, \"end\": 540.88, \"text\": \"Over the years \\\"anti-vaxers\\\" have grown in numbers.\"}, {\"start\": 540.88, \"end\": 546.2, \"text\": \"These are people who believe vaccines cause autism and other diseases and they are distrustful\"}, {\"start\": 546.2, \"end\": 548.24, \"text\": \"of the government and pharmaceutical companies.\"}, {\"start\": 548.24, \"end\": 556.32, \"text\": \"But even though several states are considering anti-vaccination bills, many lawmakers say\"}, {\"start\": 556.32, \"end\": 562.54, \"text\": \"most of those bills will be seen as a public health threat and die in committee.\"}, {\"start\": 565.34, \"end\": 567.48, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 567.48, \"end\": 569.18, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 569.18, \"end\": 571.86, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 571.86, \"end\": 576.06, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 576.06, \"end\": 577.78, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 577.78, \"end\": 579.26, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 579.3, \"end\": 582.4, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "jKhTTxkHScY": {
    "video_id": "jKhTTxkHScY",
    "title": "State of the Union preview (ASL - 1.29.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180130",
    "duration": 60,
    "view_count": 268,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.8, \"end\": 8.14, \"text\": \"President Trump will deliver his first State of the Union address to the nation and Congress\"}, {\"start\": 8.14, \"end\": 9.72, \"text\": \"Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 9.72, \"end\": 13.26, \"text\": \"At the forefront of his speech: immigration.\"}, {\"start\": 13.26, \"end\": 20.5, \"text\": \"The president tweeted late Saturday about his DACA plan.\"}, {\"start\": 20.5, \"end\": 26.26, \"text\": \"Trump tweeted: \\\"I have offered DACA a wonderful deal, including a doubling in the number of\"}, {\"start\": 26.26, \"end\": 32.36, \"text\": \"recipients and a 12 year pathway to citizenship, for two reasons: 1) because the Republicans\"}, {\"start\": 32.36, \"end\": 39.28, \"text\": \"want to fix a longtime terrible problem, 2) to show the Democrats do not want to solve\"}, {\"start\": 39.28, \"end\": 42.26, \"text\": \"DACA, only use it.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 42.26, \"end\": 47.5, \"text\": \"Trump also attacked Democrats on border safety.\"}, {\"start\": 47.5, \"end\": 51.52, \"text\": \"He tweeted: \\\"Democrats are not interested in border safety and security or in the funding\"}, {\"start\": 51.52, \"end\": 55.52, \"text\": \"and rebuilding of our military.\"}, {\"start\": 55.52, \"end\": 58.92, \"text\": \"They are only interested in obstructions.\\\"\"}]"
  },
  "l6FTtwVHFbE": {
    "video_id": "l6FTtwVHFbE",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.21.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180122",
    "duration": 397,
    "view_count": 1076,
    "description": "1.21.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Trump calls for rules change to end shutdown\n-White House phone message bashes Democrats\n-NFL streams games to troops during government shutdown\n-Mudslide death toll rises to 21\n-Rapper Fredo Santana dies at age 27\n-Nike unveils Playstation-themed basketball shoes\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information i",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.06, \"end\": 7.3, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.3, \"end\": 9.24, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.24, \"end\": 10.36, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 10.36, \"end\": 12.86, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.48, \"end\": 22.98, \"text\": \"The House and Senate were back in session today attempting to break an impasse that\"}, {\"start\": 22.98, \"end\": 25.58, \"text\": \"caused federal agencies to shut down.\"}, {\"start\": 25.58, \"end\": 29.08, \"text\": \"And there is no indication lawmakers are any closer to reaching a deal.\"}, {\"start\": 29.08, \"end\": 36.16, \"text\": \"Chamber rules require 60 votes to break the budget impasse and Senate Republicans currently\"}, {\"start\": 36.16, \"end\": 39.28, \"text\": \"have 51 votes.\"}, {\"start\": 39.3, \"end\": 48.16, \"text\": \"President Trump was up and tweeting early Sunday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 48.16, \"end\": 53.16, \"text\": \"He tweeted \\\"Great to see how hard Republicans are fighting for our military and safety at\"}, {\"start\": 53.16, \"end\": 54.68, \"text\": \"the border.\"}, {\"start\": 54.68, \"end\": 60.92, \"text\": \"The Dems just want illegal immigrants to pour into our nation unchecked.\"}, {\"start\": 60.92, \"end\": 77.76, \"text\": \"If stalemate continues, Republicans should go to 51 percent -- \\\"nuclear option\\\" -- and\"}, {\"start\": 77.76, \"end\": 85.08, \"text\": \"vote on real, long-term budget, no C.R.'s.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 88.64, \"end\": 92.84, \"text\": \"If you're upset about the government shutdown and want to leave a message on the White House\"}, {\"start\": 92.84, \"end\": 99.2, \"text\": \"comment line, here is a message you will receive:\"}, {\"start\": 99.2, \"end\": 102.16, \"text\": \"Thank you for calling the White House.\"}, {\"start\": 102.16, \"end\": 108.8, \"text\": \"Unfortunately we cannot answer your call today because Congressional Democrats are holding\"}, {\"start\": 108.84, \"end\": 113.92, \"text\": \"government funding, including funding for our troops and other national security priorities\"}, {\"start\": 113.92, \"end\": 121.72, \"text\": \"hostage to an unrelated immigration debate.\"}, {\"start\": 121.72, \"end\": 125.64, \"text\": \"Due to this obstruction, the government shutdown.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 128.04, \"end\": 133.04, \"text\": \"The Department of Defense has announced that it will continue to show sports programming\"}, {\"start\": 133.04, \"end\": 136.32, \"text\": \"during the government shutdown after receiving complaints from troops.\"}, {\"start\": 136.32, \"end\": 143.52, \"text\": \"The military's broadcast provider, the American Forces Network (AFN) closed because of the\"}, {\"start\": 143.52, \"end\": 145.48, \"text\": \"shutdown.\"}, {\"start\": 145.48, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"Complaint started coming in almost immediately, as deployed troops realize they would not\"}, {\"start\": 149.0, \"end\": 151.2, \"text\": \"be able to watch football games.\"}, {\"start\": 151.28, \"end\": 157.32, \"text\": \"The NFL stepped up with a solution, offering to give US troops access to a streaming services\"}, {\"start\": 157.32, \"end\": 163.24, \"text\": \"at USO facilities worldwide.\"}, {\"start\": 163.24, \"end\": 169.24, \"text\": \"The DOD says it will make both news and sports broadcasts available to servicemembers.\"}, {\"start\": 169.24, \"end\": 173.56, \"text\": \"The DOD also called on Congress to pass a budget.\"}, {\"start\": 176.52, \"end\": 181.84, \"text\": \"The death toll from the mudslide in California has climbed to 21.\"}, {\"start\": 181.84, \"end\": 197.36, \"text\": \"Officials say the body of 28-year-old Faviola Benitez Calderon was discovered in Montecito\"}, {\"start\": 197.36, \"end\": 198.8, \"text\": \"on Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 198.96, \"end\": 205.2, \"text\": \"Her son, niece and sister-in-law were also killed in the mudslide.\"}, {\"start\": 205.2, \"end\": 211.2, \"text\": \"The area became more prone to mudslides after massive wildfires last month.\"}, {\"start\": 211.2, \"end\": 216.52, \"text\": \"A wall of mud and debris swept through the area earlier this month after heavy rains.\"}, {\"start\": 216.52, \"end\": 226.64, \"text\": \"It destroyed dozens of homes and damaged hundreds more.\"}, {\"start\": 226.64, \"end\": 232.76, \"text\": \"Search crews are still looking for two more missing victims, including a two-year-old\"}, {\"start\": 232.76, \"end\": 234.88, \"text\": \"girl.\"}, {\"start\": 237.72, \"end\": 245.6, \"text\": \"Rapper Fredo Santana died Friday night at his Los Angeles home.\"}, {\"start\": 245.6, \"end\": 247.64, \"text\": \"He was 27 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 247.64, \"end\": 256.92, \"text\": \"In October, he posted on Instagram that he was being treated for liver and kidney failure.\"}, {\"start\": 256.92, \"end\": 267.08, \"text\": \"One of his relatives said that Santana had been sick, but did not disclose more details.\"}, {\"start\": 267.08, \"end\": 271.12, \"text\": \"And the medical examiner's office has not yet performed an autopsy.\"}, {\"start\": 271.12, \"end\": 275.96, \"text\": \"The relative also said the rapper became a father last June, when his girlfriend had\"}, {\"start\": 275.96, \"end\": 278.76, \"text\": \"a baby boy.\"}, {\"start\": 281.52, \"end\": 289.16, \"text\": \"PlayStation is the inspiration for Nike's newest basketball shoe.\"}, {\"start\": 289.32, \"end\": 296.08, \"text\": \"The \\\"P-G-2 PlayStation\\\" sneakers were unveiled on Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 296.08, \"end\": 297.24, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 322.92, \"end\": 336.28, \"text\": \"Nike, Sony PlayStation and NBA All-Star Paul George teamed up to create the custom shoes\"}, {\"start\": 336.28, \"end\": 340.16, \"text\": \"as a tribute to George's love of gaming.\"}, {\"start\": 340.16, \"end\": 345.12, \"text\": \"The shoe design has illuminating logos on the tongues that pulse when you press them.\"}, {\"start\": 345.12, \"end\": 351.44, \"text\": \"And each pair of shoes has a voucher code that can be redeemed for a special Paul George\"}, {\"start\": 351.44, \"end\": 353.92, \"text\": \"theme for your PlayStation 4.\"}, {\"start\": 353.92, \"end\": 360.44, \"text\": \"The limited-edition sneakers will be available in stores on February 10.\"}, {\"start\": 360.44, \"end\": 369.08, \"text\": \"But George debuted the shoes against the Cleveland Cavaliers Saturday night.\"}, {\"start\": 369.08, \"end\": 373.4, \"text\": \"The price tag: a little over 100 bucks.\"}, {\"start\": 376.12, \"end\": 378.52, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 378.52, \"end\": 379.88, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 379.88, \"end\": 382.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 382.0, \"end\": 386.24, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 386.24, \"end\": 392.8, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "p4eINVM_gbg": {
    "video_id": "p4eINVM_gbg",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.28.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171229",
    "duration": 502,
    "view_count": 2048,
    "description": "December 28, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-ROY MOORE COMPLAINT TO BLOCK SENATE RESULT\n-DANGER RISING FOR CHILDREN IN CONFLICT ZONES\n-NEW YEAR’S EVE SECURITY AT ALL-TIME HIGH IN LV AND NY\n-CUBAN BOY TO GET 10-LB FACE TUMOR REMOVED\n-LL COOL J: FIRST KENNEDY CTR HIP-HOP ARTIST HONOREE\n-NATURE LOVERS WATCH EAGLETS BEING HATCHED\n-POWERBALL AND MEGA-MILLIONS JACKPOTS OVER $300M\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.98, \"end\": 8.88, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.88, \"end\": 10.8, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.84, \"end\": 11.84, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 11.84, \"end\": 14.86, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.28, \"end\": 27.2, \"text\": \"On Wednesday Republican candidate Roy Moore filed a complaint in the Circuit Court of\"}, {\"start\": 27.24, \"end\": 29.26, \"text\": \"Montgomery, Alabama.\"}, {\"start\": 29.26, \"end\": 33.64, \"text\": \"He claims there may have been voter fraud.\"}, {\"start\": 33.64, \"end\": 43.12, \"text\": \"Moore is trying to stop officials from declaring Democrat Doug Jones the winner.\"}, {\"start\": 43.12, \"end\": 45.84, \"text\": \"Moore is also asking for an investigation before the election is certified.\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 52.72, \"text\": \"Moore's campaign is asking supporters to help by calling state officials.\"}, {\"start\": 52.72, \"end\": 61.12, \"text\": \"But Alabama's Secretary of State certified Jones as the winner today.\"}, {\"start\": 61.12, \"end\": 64.56, \"text\": \"Jones' campaign team released a statement as well.\"}, {\"start\": 64.8, \"end\": 69.6, \"text\": \"It said: \\\"This desperate attempt by Roy Moore to subvert the will of the people will not\"}, {\"start\": 69.6, \"end\": 70.88, \"text\": \"succeed.\"}, {\"start\": 70.88, \"end\": 74.64, \"text\": \"The election is over, it's time to move on.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 78.4, \"end\": 85.44, \"text\": \"On Wednesday, UNICEF warned that children in war zones around the world have come under\"}, {\"start\": 85.44, \"end\": 93.04, \"text\": \"attack at a shocking scale throughout the year.\"}, {\"start\": 93.04, \"end\": 99.76, \"text\": \"They said those groups involved in the wars are blatantly disregarding international laws\"}, {\"start\": 99.76, \"end\": 109.92, \"text\": \"designed to protect children.\"}, {\"start\": 109.92, \"end\": 127.12, \"text\": \"Experts say children all over the world have become front-line targets used as human shields,\"}, {\"start\": 127.12, \"end\": 134.8, \"text\": \"killed, maimed and recruited to fight.\"}, {\"start\": 135.04, \"end\": 151.6, \"text\": \"Other risks like rape, forced marriage, abduction and enslavement have become standard tactics\"}, {\"start\": 151.6, \"end\": 160.4, \"text\": \"in conflicts from Iraq, Syria, Yemen, Nigeria, South Sudan and Myanmar.\"}, {\"start\": 163.12, \"end\": 168.08, \"text\": \"New Year's Eve is three days away!\"}, {\"start\": 168.08, \"end\": 174.84, \"text\": \"And security preparations are underway in some of the country's most popular party spots\"}, {\"start\": 174.84, \"end\": 175.92, \"text\": \"right now.\"}, {\"start\": 175.92, \"end\": 184.94, \"text\": \"There will be more than 300 National Guard troops in Las Vegas this New Year's Eve, doubling\"}, {\"start\": 184.94, \"end\": 190.5, \"text\": \"the amount typically on hand.\"}, {\"start\": 190.5, \"end\": 198.379, \"text\": \"And mobile command posts will be staged throughout the city.\"}, {\"start\": 198.38, \"end\": 205.0, \"text\": \"Roughly 1,500 police officers will be patrolling the Las Vegas area over the three-day holiday\"}, {\"start\": 205.0, \"end\": 206.66, \"text\": \"weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 206.66, \"end\": 213.74, \"text\": \"Security in New York's Time Square will reach unprecedented levels this New Year's Eve.\"}, {\"start\": 213.78, \"end\": 222.18, \"text\": \"This after the city had two terror attacks within the last three months.\"}, {\"start\": 222.18, \"end\": 232.66, \"text\": \"More than 1 million people are expected to ring in the New Year in the Big Apple.\"}, {\"start\": 232.66, \"end\": 247.16, \"text\": \"Despite the increase in police, officials remind the public to report anything suspicious.\"}, {\"start\": 249.98, \"end\": 255.96, \"text\": \"Doctors in Florida are set to remove a massive tumor from the face of a Cuban teen boy.\"}, {\"start\": 255.96, \"end\": 265.74, \"text\": \"His name is Emanuel Zayas and he's 14 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 265.74, \"end\": 271.9, \"text\": \"Initially the tumor was the size of a pimple.\"}, {\"start\": 271.9, \"end\": 280.32, \"text\": \"Over the past three years it has grown to the size of a basketball, weighing roughly\"}, {\"start\": 280.32, \"end\": 283.06, \"text\": \"10 pounds.\"}, {\"start\": 283.06, \"end\": 291.62, \"text\": \"One of the doctors set to operate on Emanuel says the tumor's weight alone is life-threatening.\"}, {\"start\": 291.62, \"end\": 297.02, \"text\": \"It has also left Emanuel extremely malnourished and he is only able to breathe through his\"}, {\"start\": 297.02, \"end\": 298.76, \"text\": \"mouth.\"}, {\"start\": 298.76, \"end\": 308.26, \"text\": \"His first surgery is scheduled for January at the University of Miami Jackson Memorial\"}, {\"start\": 308.26, \"end\": 310.7, \"text\": \"Medical Center.\"}, {\"start\": 313.3, \"end\": 322.38, \"text\": \"LL Cool J is the first hip-hop artist to be included as a \\\"Kennedy Center\\\" honoree.\"}, {\"start\": 322.38, \"end\": 330.86, \"text\": \"The actor and hip-hop icon gushed with gratitude on Twitter Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 330.92, \"end\": 335.96, \"text\": \"And he is giving his fans a credit.\"}, {\"start\": 335.96, \"end\": 343.3, \"text\": \"He wrote, in part, \\\"I want to personally thank every single one of you!\"}, {\"start\": 343.38, \"end\": 348.76, \"text\": \"You bought the songs, you attended the concert!\"}, {\"start\": 348.76, \"end\": 350.6, \"text\": \"You've been with me the whole time.\"}, {\"start\": 350.6, \"end\": 352.08, \"text\": \"I love you.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 354.94, \"end\": 363.12, \"text\": \"A female bald eagle named \\\"Harriett\\\" has been nesting in North Fort Myers since 2006.\"}, {\"start\": 363.12, \"end\": 369.4, \"text\": \"Finally, the eaglets hatched from the two eggs she laid in November.\"}, {\"start\": 369.4, \"end\": 381.46, \"text\": \"Thousands of nature lovers watched via WebCam as the baby eagles hatched.\"}, {\"start\": 381.46, \"end\": 389.14, \"text\": \"\\\"E-10\\\" came into the world on Tuesday at about 8:45 PM.\"}, {\"start\": 389.14, \"end\": 396.66, \"text\": \"\\\"E-11\\\" came into the world just before 4:30 PM Wednesday afternoon.\"}, {\"start\": 396.66, \"end\": 406.8, \"text\": \"Harriett's original mate, Ozzie, died in 2015.\"}, {\"start\": 406.8, \"end\": 414.02, \"text\": \"She is now in her second meeting season with her new mate, known as M-15.\"}, {\"start\": 415.28, \"end\": 422.92, \"text\": \"If you're feeling lucky, you may want to buy a lottery ticket this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 422.96, \"end\": 433.32, \"text\": \"The Megamillions jackpot is now at $306 million and growing.\"}, {\"start\": 433.32, \"end\": 440.04, \"text\": \"The next drawing is 11 PM Eastern time on Friday night.\"}, {\"start\": 440.06, \"end\": 448.84, \"text\": \"And the Powerball jackpot has jumped to $384 million after no winners in Wednesday night's\"}, {\"start\": 448.84, \"end\": 451.2, \"text\": \"drawing.\"}, {\"start\": 451.2, \"end\": 456.6, \"text\": \"A ticket worth $2 million was sold in Georgia.\"}, {\"start\": 456.6, \"end\": 469.48, \"text\": \"The odds of winning the Powerball drawing 1 in 292.2 million.\"}, {\"start\": 469.48, \"end\": 475.06, \"text\": \"The next Powerball drawing is Saturday night.\"}, {\"start\": 475.06, \"end\": 476.82, \"text\": \"Good luck!\"}, {\"start\": 478.9, \"end\": 481.54, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 481.54, \"end\": 482.88, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 482.9, \"end\": 485.16, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 485.22, \"end\": 488.76, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 488.76, \"end\": 494.24, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "668bu_vGg7M": {
    "video_id": "668bu_vGg7M",
    "title": "Atlanta Area School for the Deaf Annual Fall Festival (ASL - 11.4.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20181105",
    "duration": 264,
    "view_count": 891,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.12, \"end\": 6.2, \"text\": \"Yesterday was a big day at Atlanta Area school for the Deaf.\"}, {\"start\": 6.2, \"end\": 12.74, \"text\": \"The school held its 26th annual fall festival.\"}, {\"start\": 12.74, \"end\": 20.42, \"text\": \"This is the school's biggest fundraiser and it brings out dozens of Deaf-friendly businesses,\"}, {\"start\": 20.42, \"end\": 23.08, \"text\": \"vendors and news organizations.\"}, {\"start\": 23.08, \"end\": 29.64, \"text\": \"Sign1News was there also to inform everyone about what we do.\"}, {\"start\": 29.64, \"end\": 38.36, \"text\": \"There was also a silent auction and Sign1News donated a special gift: become a Sign1News\"}, {\"start\": 38.36, \"end\": 42.829, \"text\": \"news anchor for a day.\"}, {\"start\": 42.829, \"end\": 50.56, \"text\": \"The winner will come into our studio to work with our staff and be showcased on one of\"}, {\"start\": 50.56, \"end\": 52.98, \"text\": \"our upcoming broadcasts.\"}, {\"start\": 52.98, \"end\": 57.52, \"text\": \"We can't wait to find out who won.\"}, {\"start\": 57.52, \"end\": 67.72, \"text\": \"Multimedia journalist Martha Anger was at the festival and captured all the fun and\"}, {\"start\": 67.72, \"end\": 71.44, \"text\": \"festivities.\"}, {\"start\": 71.44, \"end\": 74.82, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 81.7, \"end\": 88.02, \"text\": \"The halls of Atlanta Area School for the Deaf were packed this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 88.02, \"end\": 92.22, \"text\": \"Hundreds of people, including our own Sign1News anchor Crystal Cousineau, were there for the\"}, {\"start\": 92.22, \"end\": 94.08, \"text\": \"annual fall festival.\"}, {\"start\": 94.08, \"end\": 105.96, \"text\": \"This was an indoor and outdoor event with fun and games for all ages.\"}, {\"start\": 105.96, \"end\": 111.36, \"text\": \"Lots of cool items were up for grabs in the silent auction.\"}, {\"start\": 111.36, \"end\": 121.92, \"text\": \"There was so much to see, do and learn.\"}, {\"start\": 121.96, \"end\": 123.6, \"text\": \"I am an MMJ.\"}, {\"start\": 123.6, \"end\": 129.46, \"text\": \"I shoot, edit and report stories.\"}, {\"start\": 129.46, \"end\": 133.02, \"text\": \"Pretty much do everything from A-Z.\"}, {\"start\": 133.02, \"end\": 139.34, \"text\": \"My personal passion is as an actor and filmmaker.\"}, {\"start\": 139.34, \"end\": 143.54, \"text\": \"On the professional side I am an MMJ, sharing news stories.\"}, {\"start\": 144.92, \"end\": 154.18, \"text\": \"SignOn Connect is for those who want to be immersed in ASL.\"}, {\"start\": 154.18, \"end\": 156.5, \"text\": \"All of our staff is Deaf.\"}, {\"start\": 162.5, \"end\": 164.1, \"text\": \"Dozens of vendors showed off their products.\"}, {\"start\": 171.76, \"end\": 179.08, \"text\": \"I am an artist, Deaf De'Via and political artist.\"}, {\"start\": 179.1, \"end\": 181.72, \"text\": \"I'm here to sell my work.\"}, {\"start\": 181.72, \"end\": 189.82, \"text\": \"I have a few political pieces of work and 18 percent of sales will be donated to the\"}, {\"start\": 189.82, \"end\": 195.66, \"text\": \"Jewish synagogue in Pittsburgh to honor those who died.\"}, {\"start\": 195.68, \"end\": 197.94, \"text\": \"Here are the three pieces.\"}, {\"start\": 212.18, \"end\": 214.78, \"text\": \"Thank you for all of your support.\"}, {\"start\": 214.78, \"end\": 219.14, \"text\": \"I will be creating more artwork in the future.\"}, {\"start\": 221.32, \"end\": 228.4, \"text\": \"The goal of the \\\"Parent to Parent\\\" program is to involve parents and the school in partnership.\"}, {\"start\": 228.4, \"end\": 235.94, \"text\": \"We want to include parents in the Deaf community to support children's language acquisition\"}, {\"start\": 235.94, \"end\": 239.58, \"text\": \"and improve their language skills.\"}, {\"start\": 239.58, \"end\": 244.9, \"text\": \"Sign1News set up a mock studio so people could try out their news reporting skills.\"}, {\"start\": 244.9, \"end\": 251.04, \"text\": \"Hello everyone my name is Joaquin.\"}, {\"start\": 257.64, \"end\": 259.02, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 259.02, \"end\": 260.32, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 260.32, \"end\": 263.66, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "7iwfFafwIyo": {
    "video_id": "7iwfFafwIyo",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.27.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171227",
    "duration": 658,
    "view_count": 743,
    "description": "December 27, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-10 DEAD FROM FAKE ALCOHOL POISONING\n-ARGENTINE PROSECUTOR’S DEATH RULED A MURDER\n-PRINCE HARRY SIDESTEPS OBAMA WEDDING INVITE QUESTION\n-MORE PREGNANT WOMEN SMOKING POT\n-REPAINTING THE VATICAN WITH MILK\n-PROTECTING YOUR GIFT CARDS\n-TIME LAPSE OF RECORD SNOWFALL IN ERIE, PA\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.86, \"end\": 6.64, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.64, \"end\": 8.36, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.36, \"end\": 9.38, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 9.38, \"end\": 11.58, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 13.64, \"end\": 21.28, \"text\": \"The Dominican Republic is under a public health alert after authorities revealed at least\"}, {\"start\": 21.3, \"end\": 25.66, \"text\": \"10 cases of deadly alcohol poisoning.\"}, {\"start\": 25.66, \"end\": 38.12, \"text\": \"The deaths are a direct result of consuming homemade alcoholic beverages containing methanol.\"}, {\"start\": 38.12, \"end\": 45.94, \"text\": \"The country usually sees an uptick in drinking during the holiday season as lower income\"}, {\"start\": 45.98, \"end\": 58.2, \"text\": \"families are more tempted to buy this toxic product due to its cheaper price.\"}, {\"start\": 58.2, \"end\": 66.96, \"text\": \"Public health officials urge people to abstain from drinking this product which is produced\"}, {\"start\": 66.96, \"end\": 73.2, \"text\": \"under poor sanitary conditions.\"}, {\"start\": 75.16, \"end\": 85.04, \"text\": \"According to a federal judge, Argentine prosecutor Alberto NIsman, who accused top government\"}, {\"start\": 85.04, \"end\": 88.52, \"text\": \"officials of a cover-up in the country's deadliest terror attack, was murdered.\"}, {\"start\": 88.56, \"end\": 92.8, \"text\": \"Nisman was found dead in his Buenos Aries apartment on January 29, 2015.\"}, {\"start\": 92.96, \"end\": 95.56, \"text\": \"He'd been shot in the head.\"}, {\"start\": 95.56, \"end\": 104.68, \"text\": \"His death had originally been ruled a suicide but investigators found no gunshot powder\"}, {\"start\": 104.68, \"end\": 113.28, \"text\": \"residue on his hands.\"}, {\"start\": 113.4, \"end\": 121.64, \"text\": \"A few days earlier Nisman had filed a report accusing Argentina's former president and\"}, {\"start\": 121.64, \"end\": 152.4, \"text\": \"other officials of covering up Iran's involvement in the 1994 Jewish community center bombing\"}, {\"start\": 152.4, \"end\": 161.96, \"text\": \"that left 85 people dead and more than 300 wounded.\"}, {\"start\": 161.96, \"end\": 170.68, \"text\": \"But the night he was scheduled to testify before lawmakers, his body was found.\"}, {\"start\": 172.96, \"end\": 181.28, \"text\": \"Prince Harry and Meghan Markle haven't even printed wedding invitations yet and already there\"}, {\"start\": 181.28, \"end\": 185.52, \"text\": \"is trouble brewing over the ceremony.\"}, {\"start\": 185.52, \"end\": 193.72, \"text\": \"And it involves former President Barack Obama and President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 194.08, \"end\": 198.96, \"text\": \"Prince Harry and Obama have become good friends over the years.\"}, {\"start\": 198.96, \"end\": 205.0, \"text\": \"Prince Harry has made it clear he wants the Obama's at his wedding.\"}, {\"start\": 205.0, \"end\": 213.36, \"text\": \"But the British government fears inviting the Obama's and not inviting President Trump\"}, {\"start\": 213.36, \"end\": 219.68, \"text\": \"will cause an uproar and damage the relationship between the United States and England.\"}, {\"start\": 219.68, \"end\": 226.88, \"text\": \"Prince Harry \\\"somewhat\\\" address the issue today during an interview with the BBC.\"}, {\"start\": 226.88, \"end\": 231.36, \"text\": \"Here's what he said about his relationship with Obama.\"}, {\"start\": 244.8, \"end\": 249.76, \"text\": \"During the interview he was asked \\\"Well enough to invite him to your wedding?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 249.92, \"end\": 253.04, \"text\": \"Prince Harry said \\\"Well, I don't know about that.\"}, {\"start\": 253.04, \"end\": 256.92, \"text\": \"We haven't put the invites or the guestlist together yet so who knows whether he's going\"}, {\"start\": 256.92, \"end\": 260.4, \"text\": \"to be invited or not.\"}, {\"start\": 260.48, \"end\": 262.76, \"text\": \"I wouldn't want to ruin that surprise.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 265.62, \"end\": 272.9, \"text\": \"There is a new study out suggesting that more pregnant women appear to be using marijuana\"}, {\"start\": 272.9, \"end\": 276.819, \"text\": \"to soothe anxiety and morning sickness.\"}, {\"start\": 276.82, \"end\": 285.36, \"text\": \"The study was published Tuesday in the \\\"Journal of American Medical Association.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 285.36, \"end\": 290.46, \"text\": \"The study observed a sample of pregnant women in California.\"}, {\"start\": 290.46, \"end\": 303.06, \"text\": \"Pot use among the women climbed from 4.2% to 7.1% from 2009 through 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 303.06, \"end\": 308.84, \"text\": \"One expert speculates that the rise might be partially explained by the increased availability\"}, {\"start\": 308.84, \"end\": 315.7, \"text\": \"of legal marijuana in recent years.\"}, {\"start\": 315.7, \"end\": 323.12, \"text\": \"But doctors warned that marijuana's effect on a fetus aren't clear and could cause low\"}, {\"start\": 323.12, \"end\": 327.52, \"text\": \"birth weight and developmental problems.\"}, {\"start\": 329.3, \"end\": 339.4, \"text\": \"You might think that restoring a 500-year-old building would require high-tech solutions.\"}, {\"start\": 339.4, \"end\": 355.04, \"text\": \"But at the Vatican, they do things the old-fashioned way: using milk to repaint the Belvedere Palace.\"}, {\"start\": 355.04, \"end\": 360.68, \"text\": \"It's an ancient recipe that has proven more lasting than any modern synthetic paints.\"}, {\"start\": 360.68, \"end\": 366.06, \"text\": \"They get the milk from the Pope's cows.\"}, {\"start\": 366.1, \"end\": 376.16, \"text\": \"The milk is mixed with slaked lime and the original cream-color use in the 1500s.\"}, {\"start\": 376.16, \"end\": 383.28, \"text\": \"Then it is hand patted onto the walls in a centuries-old technique.\"}, {\"start\": 383.28, \"end\": 396.54, \"text\": \"So in a world where the computer can do most anything, at the Vatican, the hands of workers\"}, {\"start\": 396.54, \"end\": 401.5, \"text\": \"and mother nature still work.\"}, {\"start\": 403.2, \"end\": 410.46, \"text\": \"If you received a gift card during the holidays, listen up.\"}, {\"start\": 410.46, \"end\": 421.82, \"text\": \"\\\"Consumer Reports\\\" is out with a new warning on how crooks can scan money from those cards.\"}, {\"start\": 421.82, \"end\": 437.12, \"text\": \"The scam can be as simple as the crook taking the card from the rack, writing down the numbers\"}, {\"start\": 437.12, \"end\": 444.58, \"text\": \"and scratching off the strip on the back to get the security codes.\"}, {\"start\": 444.58, \"end\": 454.66, \"text\": \"Then the thief covers the codes with replacement strips and leaves the store.\"}, {\"start\": 454.72, \"end\": 466.46, \"text\": \"Once you buy the card and load money onto it, the thief gets an alert and uses up the\"}, {\"start\": 466.46, \"end\": 470.32, \"text\": \"money before you do.\"}, {\"start\": 470.32, \"end\": 477.9, \"text\": \"\\\"Consumer Reports\\\" recommends protecting yourself by buying directly from the retailer online.\"}, {\"start\": 477.9, \"end\": 486.1, \"text\": \"And if you do buy a gift card in person from a store, try to get one that is behind the\"}, {\"start\": 486.1, \"end\": 488.06, \"text\": \"register.\"}, {\"start\": 488.12, \"end\": 497.7, \"text\": \"If you are the victim of a scam, it may help to call the retailer who issued the card.\"}, {\"start\": 497.74, \"end\": 503.26, \"text\": \"They may help identify the fraud and refund your money.\"}, {\"start\": 503.26, \"end\": 515.32, \"text\": \"You can get more details by checking out the full article on www.ConsumerReports.org.\"}, {\"start\": 517.12, \"end\": 524.34, \"text\": \"The town of Erie, Pennsylvania experienced two record-breaking days of snowfall.\"}, {\"start\": 524.34, \"end\": 530.78, \"text\": \"On Monday, 34 inches of snow fell on the town.\"}, {\"start\": 530.78, \"end\": 535.72, \"text\": \"That's more than four times the previous Christmas Day record.\"}, {\"start\": 535.72, \"end\": 546.18, \"text\": \"On Tuesday, another 20 inches fell by the afternoon, covering Erie with 54 1/2 inches\"}, {\"start\": 546.18, \"end\": 548.26, \"text\": \"of snow in just two days.\"}, {\"start\": 548.26, \"end\": 555.46, \"text\": \"City police declared a snow emergency and they're asking people to stay off the roads.\"}, {\"start\": 555.46, \"end\": 561.3, \"text\": \"According to the National Weather Service, the area can expect the snow to continue through\"}, {\"start\": 561.3, \"end\": 563.08, \"text\": \"Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 563.08, \"end\": 571.02, \"text\": \"Thanks to the \\\"Epic Web Studios\\\" we have amazing time-lapsed video of the snow -- from the\"}, {\"start\": 571.02, \"end\": 574.14, \"text\": \"moment it started to the time it finished.\"}, {\"start\": 574.14, \"end\": 576.16, \"text\": \"Watch this.\"}, {\"start\": 636.76, \"end\": 638.82, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 638.82, \"end\": 640.12, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 640.12, \"end\": 642.36, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 642.42, \"end\": 646.36, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 646.4, \"end\": 651.68, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "BlzpvIPLg1w": {
    "video_id": "BlzpvIPLg1w",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.14.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180414",
    "duration": 1033,
    "view_count": 3257,
    "description": "4.14.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Trump declares “mission accomplished” in Syria\n-Historic wildfires raging in Oklahoma\n-Tornado forms in Moutainburg, Arkansas\n-Jennifer Hart had alcohol in system at time of fatal crash\n-Butt-breathing turtle with funk rock haircut\n-Deaf world-traveler Calvin Young visits Sign1News\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have back",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.56, \"end\": 9.2, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.2, \"end\": 11.42, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.42, \"end\": 12.74, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 12.74, \"end\": 16.18, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.22, \"end\": 28.42, \"text\": \"Last night President Trump announced that the United States, France and the United Kingdom\"}, {\"start\": 28.42, \"end\": 39.96, \"text\": \"had launched coordinated air and ground strikes on Syria.\"}, {\"start\": 39.96, \"end\": 44.08, \"text\": \"The strikes were in retaliation for an alleged chemical weapons attack on innocent citizens\"}, {\"start\": 44.08, \"end\": 51.81, \"text\": \"by the Syrian government last week.\"}, {\"start\": 51.84, \"end\": 56.88, \"text\": \"The chemical attack left dozens of men, women and children dead.\"}, {\"start\": 56.88, \"end\": 64.4, \"text\": \"Today Trump said the military strikes were executed perfectly and the mission was accomplished.\"}, {\"start\": 64.4, \"end\": 78.56, \"text\": \"The sites targeted were a chemical warfare technology center in the Damascus area, a\"}, {\"start\": 78.56, \"end\": 90.88, \"text\": \"chemical weapons storage site west of Homs and a nearby command post, which was also\"}, {\"start\": 90.88, \"end\": 95.14, \"text\": \"a chemical weapons storage site.\"}, {\"start\": 95.159, \"end\": 102.84, \"text\": \"Officials say the strikes are meant to deter the future use of chemical weapons and they\"}, {\"start\": 102.84, \"end\": 107.2, \"text\": \"come one year after a similar set of target strikes in 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 107.2, \"end\": 112.8, \"text\": \"For now Pentagon officials say this was a one time shot.\"}, {\"start\": 112.8, \"end\": 115.36, \"text\": \"But they are prepared for it not to be the last.\"}, {\"start\": 115.36, \"end\": 124.4, \"text\": \"We also learned today that President Trump ordered the military strikes without the authorization\"}, {\"start\": 124.4, \"end\": 136.24, \"text\": \"or approval of Congress.\"}, {\"start\": 136.24, \"end\": 141.2, \"text\": \"Several lawmakers blasted Trump for not consulting the Constitution before making his decision.\"}, {\"start\": 144.96, \"end\": 159.8, \"text\": \"The entire town of Vici, Oklahoma has been evacuated due to a blazing wildfire.\"}, {\"start\": 159.8, \"end\": 168.0, \"text\": \"Three homes have been destroyed and about 800 homes are in the path of the flames.\"}, {\"start\": 168.0, \"end\": 181.2, \"text\": \"In neighboring Woodward County, more than 100,000 acres have been scorched.\"}, {\"start\": 181.2, \"end\": 185.08, \"text\": \"Hundreds of residents have been evacuated.\"}, {\"start\": 185.08, \"end\": 194.24, \"text\": \"Police believe the fire has caused more damage in areas they can't access.\"}, {\"start\": 194.24, \"end\": 206.44, \"text\": \"By late Thursday it had burned 19,000 acres and was only 20% contained.\"}, {\"start\": 206.44, \"end\": 215.12, \"text\": \"Today firefighters are facing tough weather conditions.\"}, {\"start\": 215.12, \"end\": 226.36, \"text\": \"Some areas have gone 185 days without rainfall so the area is very dry.\"}, {\"start\": 226.36, \"end\": 234.8, \"text\": \"And winds are expected to pick up and will make controlling the flames even tougher.\"}, {\"start\": 237.96, \"end\": 249.64, \"text\": \"Two college students say they were in a car on their way to Texas when they recorded a\"}, {\"start\": 249.64, \"end\": 256.32, \"text\": \"tornado hit Mountainburg, Arkansas.\"}, {\"start\": 267.16, \"end\": 276.36, \"text\": \"The students say they passed through the storm in less than a minute and then continued toward Texas.\"}, {\"start\": 276.44, \"end\": 281.8, \"text\": \"The National Weather Service confirmed a tornado did touched down near the city.\"}, {\"start\": 281.8, \"end\": 288.56, \"text\": \"The mayor says the storm destroyed or damaged several homes, injuring one person.\"}, {\"start\": 291.22, \"end\": 301.16, \"text\": \"Officials with the California Highway Patrol say Jennifer Hart, the mother who drove her\"}, {\"start\": 301.16, \"end\": 317.94, \"text\": \"entire family off a cliff, had a blood alcohol level over the state's legal limit.\"}, {\"start\": 317.94, \"end\": 334.08, \"text\": \"Hart, her wife Sarah and three of their six children were all killed.\"}, {\"start\": 334.08, \"end\": 343.84, \"text\": \"An autopsy revealed the children had a drug in their system that causes drowsiness.\"}, {\"start\": 343.84, \"end\": 349.34, \"text\": \"The couple's other three children are missing but investigators believe they were also in\"}, {\"start\": 349.36, \"end\": 353.28, \"text\": \"the SUV at the time of the crash.\"}, {\"start\": 353.28, \"end\": 362.04, \"text\": \"A body that may be one of the missing children was discovered on April 7.\"}, {\"start\": 362.04, \"end\": 370.54, \"text\": \"An autopsy is being conducted to confirm the identity.\"}, {\"start\": 370.54, \"end\": 379.06, \"text\": \"Investigators still have not come up with a motive for the crash but they say it appears\"}, {\"start\": 379.06, \"end\": 390.4, \"text\": \"to be intentional because there were no skid marks at the scene.\"}, {\"start\": 392.28, \"end\": 396.76, \"text\": \"Here's something that you don't see every day.\"}, {\"start\": 396.88, \"end\": 403.94, \"text\": \"A butt-breathing turtle with a punk rock haircut.\"}, {\"start\": 404.0, \"end\": 411.54, \"text\": \"Yes, everything I just said is a real thing.\"}, {\"start\": 411.54, \"end\": 429.88, \"text\": \"The Mary River turtle is native to Australia and can stay underwater for up to three days\"}, {\"start\": 429.88, \"end\": 440.44, \"text\": \"using its unique ability to breathe through a reproductive opening in its posterior.\"}, {\"start\": 440.44, \"end\": 453.44, \"text\": \"It also has spikes on its chin and green algae on his head resembling a punk rock hairdo.\"}, {\"start\": 453.44, \"end\": 461.86, \"text\": \"This turtle is considered an endangered species.\"}, {\"start\": 461.86, \"end\": 478.06, \"text\": \"Biologists say some people started trading them as pets and it led to the loss of an\"}, {\"start\": 478.06, \"end\": 481.8, \"text\": \"entire generation of Mary River turtles.\"}, {\"start\": 484.22, \"end\": 491.68, \"text\": \"Deaf world traveler Calvin Young stopped by our Sign1News studio this week as part of\"}, {\"start\": 491.68, \"end\": 495.84, \"text\": \"his adventures in Atlanta.\"}, {\"start\": 495.84, \"end\": 501.4, \"text\": \"Sign1News will be featured in one of his upcoming travel segments.\"}, {\"start\": 501.4, \"end\": 507.28, \"text\": \"Since he was here, we decided to feature him on our newscast to learn more about him and\"}, {\"start\": 507.28, \"end\": 510.9, \"text\": \"his inspiration for traveling the world.\"}, {\"start\": 510.9, \"end\": 518.58, \"text\": \"Here's his interview with Sign1News anchor Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 518.58, \"end\": 522.14, \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"}, {\"start\": 526.56, \"end\": 527.6, \"text\": \"Hello everyone!\"}, {\"start\": 527.6, \"end\": 530.26, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau with Sign1News I'm here with...\"}, {\"start\": 530.26, \"end\": 530.82, \"text\": \"Hello!\"}, {\"start\": 530.82, \"end\": 534.06, \"text\": \"I'm Calvin Young.\"}, {\"start\": 534.1, \"end\": 539.78, \"text\": \"I \\\"seek the world\\\" and my travels have brought me here to Atlanta.\"}, {\"start\": 539.84, \"end\": 544.2, \"text\": \"We are so fortunate to have this opportunity to chat with Calvin.\"}, {\"start\": 544.209, \"end\": 552.61, \"text\": \"He has already interviewed us so now we are interviewing him.\"}, {\"start\": 552.61, \"end\": 555.54, \"text\": \"So why are you here in Atlanta?\"}, {\"start\": 555.54, \"end\": 560.48, \"text\": \"I've always wanted to visit Atlanta.\"}, {\"start\": 560.48, \"end\": 565.46, \"text\": \"It has the biggest and busiest airport in the world.\"}, {\"start\": 565.54, \"end\": 569.12, \"text\": \"I've always had layovers here but this time I said why not stay for a while, walk around\"}, {\"start\": 569.12, \"end\": 576.94, \"text\": \"the city, check out some of the sites, like the Varsity and eat the hot dogs.\"}, {\"start\": 576.98, \"end\": 579.3, \"text\": \"President Obama ate there too.\"}, {\"start\": 579.3, \"end\": 580.18, \"text\": \"That's right.\"}, {\"start\": 580.18, \"end\": 582.88, \"text\": \"Everyone's always talking about that.\"}, {\"start\": 582.98, \"end\": 587.4, \"text\": \"I visited the Georgia Aquarium in the World of Coke.\"}, {\"start\": 587.4, \"end\": 589.26, \"text\": \"I enjoyed sampling the different flavors.\"}, {\"start\": 589.26, \"end\": 592.0, \"text\": \"Some of them had a weird taste.\"}, {\"start\": 592.0, \"end\": 595.54, \"text\": \"The worst one was Beverly from Italy.\"}, {\"start\": 595.54, \"end\": 597.96, \"text\": \"My ancestors are from Italy.\"}, {\"start\": 597.96, \"end\": 603.4, \"text\": \"I need to contact officials there and tell them to come up with a new drink.\"}, {\"start\": 605.28, \"end\": 612.36, \"text\": \"So where are your world travels taking you next?\"}, {\"start\": 612.5, \"end\": 617.12, \"text\": \"My goal is to visit several American cities.\"}, {\"start\": 617.12, \"end\": 627.54, \"text\": \"When I leave here, I will visit Ruby Falls' Rock City in Tennessee, then on to Kentucky\"}, {\"start\": 627.6, \"end\": 629.84, \"text\": \"and I have a speaking engagement in Indiana.\"}, {\"start\": 629.84, \"end\": 633.54, \"text\": \"Then during the summer I will travel out west with my girlfriend.\"}, {\"start\": 633.54, \"end\": 635.14, \"text\": \"Just out west?\"}, {\"start\": 635.14, \"end\": 641.32, \"text\": \"I enjoy traveling all over the during the summer I can explore mountains and then when\"}, {\"start\": 641.5, \"end\": 646.1, \"text\": \"I get to the top is not freezing.\"}, {\"start\": 646.1, \"end\": 650.68, \"text\": \"I want to visit all the states on the East Coast to try and beat my dad.\"}, {\"start\": 650.68, \"end\": 651.66, \"text\": \"He has traveled to 49 states.\"}, {\"start\": 651.66, \"end\": 653.76, \"text\": \"I've only visited 46.\"}, {\"start\": 653.76, \"end\": 656.7, \"text\": \"My goal is to beat him this year.\"}, {\"start\": 656.7, \"end\": 658.34, \"text\": \"You mentioned a girlfriend.\"}, {\"start\": 658.34, \"end\": 659.28, \"text\": \"Where is she?\"}, {\"start\": 659.28, \"end\": 660.52, \"text\": \"She's right here there.\"}, {\"start\": 660.52, \"end\": 662.34, \"text\": \"She a little shy.\"}, {\"start\": 664.6, \"end\": 666.74, \"text\": \"We just wanted to show her quickly.\"}, {\"start\": 666.74, \"end\": 674.58, \"text\": \"So you mentioned you're traveling out west using what, a van or RV?\"}, {\"start\": 674.58, \"end\": 682.68, \"text\": \"For the past three years I've traveled by air, boat and backpacked.\"}, {\"start\": 682.68, \"end\": 686.139, \"text\": \"But this year it's time for me to do something different and cool.\"}, {\"start\": 686.14, \"end\": 692.74, \"text\": \"I've slept in different hotels, different beds, bathed in different showers, hung around different\"}, {\"start\": 692.74, \"end\": 698.28, \"text\": \"people with different languages, ate different foods -- nonstop.\"}, {\"start\": 698.28, \"end\": 699.42, \"text\": \"I was like \\\"Whoa!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 699.42, \"end\": 701.86, \"text\": \"I enjoyed it but I need to settle down a bit.\"}, {\"start\": 701.86, \"end\": 706.54, \"text\": \"Now I want to get in a van, go camping, focus on the deaf community.\"}, {\"start\": 706.56, \"end\": 707.66, \"text\": \"For example I'm meeting you.\"}, {\"start\": 707.66, \"end\": 712.66, \"text\": \"That's why this year I want to focus on America and see what America has to offer.\"}, {\"start\": 712.78, \"end\": 713.5, \"text\": \"My home.\"}, {\"start\": 713.5, \"end\": 715.08, \"text\": \"There's so much to show.\"}, {\"start\": 715.08, \"end\": 716.06, \"text\": \"Where are you from?\"}, {\"start\": 716.06, \"end\": 717.12, \"text\": \"Texas!\"}, {\"start\": 717.18, \"end\": 718.38, \"text\": \"Cowboy country.\"}, {\"start\": 718.4, \"end\": 721.76, \"text\": \"I was born in California, near LA.\"}, {\"start\": 721.76, \"end\": 727.54, \"text\": \"My parents stayed there for the first two years of my life and moved to Austin, Texas.\"}, {\"start\": 727.54, \"end\": 732.72, \"text\": \"My mother's side of the family is Deaf so we moved to Texas and we've been there ever since.\"}, {\"start\": 732.78, \"end\": 741.22, \"text\": \"So what inspired you to launch \\\"Seek The World?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 741.22, \"end\": 747.04, \"text\": \"Ever since I was a kid I've enjoy seeing and learning new things.\"}, {\"start\": 747.14, \"end\": 754.48, \"text\": \"I wanted to become a writer, artist, investor, lawyer -- you name it.\"}, {\"start\": 754.48, \"end\": 757.98, \"text\": \"I just soaked it all in.\"}, {\"start\": 757.98, \"end\": 759.9, \"text\": \"Plus my parents love to travel.\"}, {\"start\": 760.18, \"end\": 762.12, \"text\": \"I watched my parents traveling and that inspired me to do the same.\"}, {\"start\": 762.12, \"end\": 766.4, \"text\": \"When I was in high school I went to London.\"}, {\"start\": 766.62, \"end\": 769.12, \"text\": \"It was a wonderful experience.\"}, {\"start\": 769.12, \"end\": 770.9, \"text\": \"It truly opened my eyes.\"}, {\"start\": 770.96, \"end\": 776.3, \"text\": \"Books, the internet and pictures don't have any life.\"}, {\"start\": 776.34, \"end\": 779.3, \"text\": \"I didn't grasp much from just reading the words.\"}, {\"start\": 779.3, \"end\": 781.56, \"text\": \"I learn more by actually seeing things and being involved myself.\"}, {\"start\": 781.56, \"end\": 783.52, \"text\": \"So back to the point.\"}, {\"start\": 783.52, \"end\": 786.56, \"text\": \"The school trip in London.\"}, {\"start\": 786.56, \"end\": 792.08, \"text\": \"I went to Gallaudet, graduated from RIT and started my own real estate business with seven\"}, {\"start\": 792.08, \"end\": 796.72, \"text\": \"deaf employees but I wasn't happy.\"}, {\"start\": 796.72, \"end\": 805.52, \"text\": \"I started reading a lot about Richard Branson of Virgin Airlines, Steve Jobs, GoPro and\"}, {\"start\": 805.52, \"end\": 812.64, \"text\": \"many more books that all had something in common -- travel will help you discover your\"}, {\"start\": 812.64, \"end\": 815.68, \"text\": \"own passion and what that means to you.\"}, {\"start\": 815.68, \"end\": 816.9, \"text\": \"And it has nothing to do with money.\"}, {\"start\": 816.9, \"end\": 820.0, \"text\": \"Up to that point I thought making money meant success.\"}, {\"start\": 820.0, \"end\": 822.04, \"text\": \"I needed to live life itself.\"}, {\"start\": 822.04, \"end\": 822.86, \"text\": \"I took a two month break.\"}, {\"start\": 822.9, \"end\": 825.6, \"text\": \"I let everyone know I was done with real estate and started traveling.\"}, {\"start\": 825.66, \"end\": 827.84, \"text\": \"But after the two months, I came back and realized I wanted to travel more.\"}, {\"start\": 827.84, \"end\": 828.72, \"text\": \"But how?\"}, {\"start\": 828.72, \"end\": 829.7, \"text\": \"That was the big question.\"}, {\"start\": 829.7, \"end\": 831.02, \"text\": \"Some people I met approached me.\"}, {\"start\": 831.04, \"end\": 835.36, \"text\": \"They said I already had skills in sign language, photography, videography and some one suggested\"}, {\"start\": 835.36, \"end\": 837.12, \"text\": \"it would be cool to offer content for a deaf audience.\"}, {\"start\": 837.12, \"end\": 838.42, \"text\": \"Some have never traveled before.\"}, {\"start\": 838.42, \"end\": 844.64, \"text\": \"I said okay and went ahead and launched Seek The World for one year and that was it.\"}, {\"start\": 844.64, \"end\": 847.68, \"text\": \"I started traveling and, of course, fell in love with it.\"}, {\"start\": 847.68, \"end\": 853.12, \"text\": \"People enjoyed it and now three years later here we are.\"}, {\"start\": 853.12, \"end\": 861.44, \"text\": \"You said that you traveled from London then decided to start Seek The World.\"}, {\"start\": 861.44, \"end\": 869.6, \"text\": \"I know nothing is free. Well... camping is free.\"}, {\"start\": 869.6, \"end\": 874.24, \"text\": \"How do you pay for all the travel, food, etc.?\"}, {\"start\": 874.24, \"end\": 877.12, \"text\": \"I robbed a bank.\"}, {\"start\": 877.12, \"end\": 878.56, \"text\": \"No just kidding.\"}, {\"start\": 878.56, \"end\": 884.32, \"text\": \"First I saved a lot of money to start Seek The World.\"}, {\"start\": 884.32, \"end\": 888.32, \"text\": \"The first couple of years I didn't make a lot of money so I focused on traveling to\"}, {\"start\": 888.32, \"end\": 889.42, \"text\": \"inexpensive countries.\"}, {\"start\": 889.44, \"end\": 894.24, \"text\": \"Like in India a whole meal cost maybe two dollars, three dollars for a place to sleep,\"}, {\"start\": 894.24, \"end\": 897.68, \"text\": \"and an 18 hour train ride might cost $10.\"}, {\"start\": 897.68, \"end\": 900.64, \"text\": \"So I could afford it with the money I saved.\"}, {\"start\": 900.64, \"end\": 907.36, \"text\": \"At the same time my audience started to grow but I had a strict budget and I couldn't afford\"}, {\"start\": 907.36, \"end\": 911.52, \"text\": \"to go to the popular places like Australia, New Zealand and my dream of going to Europe.\"}, {\"start\": 911.52, \"end\": 913.04, \"text\": \"Like the fancy countries.\"}, {\"start\": 913.04, \"end\": 918.64, \"text\": \"I started earning money when a company contacted me and asked if I could sell my really good pictures.\"}, {\"start\": 918.64, \"end\": 920.8, \"text\": \"The money I earned selling the pictures helped me raise money.\"}, {\"start\": 920.8, \"end\": 931.68, \"text\": \"Also the company paid for my video footage and that helped me raise money too.\"}, {\"start\": 931.68, \"end\": 933.84, \"text\": \"It's a big difference this year.\"}, {\"start\": 933.84, \"end\": 940.8, \"text\": \"I'm being funded by Sorensen VRS and I speak at schools all over the world.\"}, {\"start\": 940.8, \"end\": 945.36, \"text\": \"Most of them enjoy what I have to say so they pay me and that allows me to continue to share\"}, {\"start\": 945.36, \"end\": 947.92, \"text\": \"my travel experiences.\"}, {\"start\": 947.92, \"end\": 953.72, \"text\": \"Has anyone ever told you that your travel experiences have inspired them to do the same?\"}, {\"start\": 953.72, \"end\": 954.44, \"text\": \"Yes.\"}, {\"start\": 954.44, \"end\": 958.56, \"text\": \"There was one woman who watched my videos and decided she would travel alone too.\"}, {\"start\": 958.56, \"end\": 960.96, \"text\": \"Others have reached out to me and told me they really enjoy what I do.\"}, {\"start\": 960.96, \"end\": 966.56, \"text\": \"One person was debating whether to go to college or travel first.\"}, {\"start\": 966.56, \"end\": 975.38, \"text\": \"They saw my adventures, how I found my passion, how it opened my eyes to something meaningful in life.\"}, {\"start\": 975.42, \"end\": 979.58, \"text\": \"So they decided to travel first and then come back to figure what to do next.\"}, {\"start\": 979.58, \"end\": 981.54, \"text\": \"That truly inspired me.\"}, {\"start\": 981.54, \"end\": 984.64, \"text\": \"Hope to hear more from you.\"}, {\"start\": 984.68, \"end\": 987.76, \"text\": \"Has he inspired you to travel?\"}, {\"start\": 987.76, \"end\": 989.96, \"text\": \"You've inspired me to go to the park.\"}, {\"start\": 989.96, \"end\": 994.36, \"text\": \"Come on! Let's go!\"}, {\"start\": 994.36, \"end\": 996.68, \"text\": \"Thank you for your time.\"}, {\"start\": 996.68, \"end\": 1003.9, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau with Sign1News interviewing Calvin Young.\"}, {\"start\": 1005.14, \"end\": 1008.36, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 1008.36, \"end\": 1009.78, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 1009.78, \"end\": 1012.5, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 1012.58, \"end\": 1018.74, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 1018.74, \"end\": 1021.18, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 1021.28, \"end\": 1023.08, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 1023.08, \"end\": 1025.92, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "mIbhXbrdfEw": {
    "video_id": "mIbhXbrdfEw",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.26.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171227",
    "duration": 688,
    "view_count": 963,
    "description": "December 26, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-SNOW, COLD TEMPS ACROSS THE NATION\n-FIRST LADY MELANIA TRUMP TWEETS CHRISTMAS SELFIE\n-LAB IN CHINA CLONES PUPPIES\n-500-YEAR OLD VATICAN MYSTERY SOLVED\n-GAMING DISORDER: NEW MENTAL HEALTH CONDITION\n-TIPS ON CHRISTMAS GIFT RETURNS\n-FRIENDS TURN OUT TO BE BROTHERS\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and inform",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.38, \"end\": 6.04, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.04, \"end\": 7.7, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 7.7, \"end\": 8.8, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 8.8, \"end\": 11.5, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 13.48, \"end\": 18.72, \"text\": \"A blast of winter weather was felt across much of the United States on Christmas, and\"}, {\"start\": 18.72, \"end\": 22.96, \"text\": \"for some areas, that will remain throughout the new year.\"}, {\"start\": 22.96, \"end\": 31.6, \"text\": \"The blustery front hit much of the top half of the United States on Christmas.\"}, {\"start\": 31.84, \"end\": 38.4, \"text\": \"Boston was among the areas pounded with a blast of frigid, snowy conditions.\"}, {\"start\": 38.4, \"end\": 46.72, \"text\": \"The DOT in Boston asked people to stay off the roads Christmas Day.\"}, {\"start\": 46.8, \"end\": 52.88, \"text\": \"Several inches of snow fell in Washington State and that led to slick roads and numerous\"}, {\"start\": 52.88, \"end\": 55.12, \"text\": \"crashes.\"}, {\"start\": 55.2, \"end\": 63.28, \"text\": \"The highs in Chicago will remain well below freezing into the new year.\"}, {\"start\": 63.36, \"end\": 73.44, \"text\": \"A \\\"code blue\\\" alert is issued in Baltimore through Thursday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 73.6, \"end\": 86.48, \"text\": \"That's a city wide effort to limit hypothermia deaths in winter.\"}, {\"start\": 86.48, \"end\": 94.32, \"text\": \"The National Weather Service says heavy snow will continue to fall in the Great Lakes,\"}, {\"start\": 94.32, \"end\": 103.52, \"text\": \"Rockies and Northeast during the last week of the year.\"}, {\"start\": 103.68, \"end\": 109.44, \"text\": \"And the windchill will continue to be a factor through Friday, with a number of cities not\"}, {\"start\": 109.44, \"end\": 111.92, \"text\": \"rising above the freezing mark.\"}, {\"start\": 111.92, \"end\": 120.8, \"text\": \"So if you're heading outside of the house, make sure you dress appropriately.\"}, {\"start\": 124.32, \"end\": 134.96, \"text\": \"First Lady Melania Trump is feeling the holiday spirit at Mar-A-Lago.\"}, {\"start\": 134.96, \"end\": 143.92, \"text\": \"She posted this selfie on Twitter Monday, with a Santa hat and lit up reindeers.\"}, {\"start\": 143.92, \"end\": 149.6, \"text\": \"Her caption reads \\\"Merry Christmas.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 149.84, \"end\": 157.84, \"text\": \"President Trump and his family are spending the holidays at his resort in Palm Beach,\"}, {\"start\": 157.84, \"end\": 161.84, \"text\": \"Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 161.92, \"end\": 167.2, \"text\": \"That includes most of the president's children and grandchildren, along with the first lady's\"}, {\"start\": 167.2, \"end\": 169.92, \"text\": \"parents.\"}, {\"start\": 169.92, \"end\": 179.76, \"text\": \"On Christmas Eve, the first couple attended service at the nearby Bethesdsa-By-The-Sea\"}, {\"start\": 179.76, \"end\": 188.32, \"text\": \"church, where they tied the knot 12 years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 190.8, \"end\": 200.0, \"text\": \"A lab in China is cloning puppies.\"}, {\"start\": 200.0, \"end\": 208.72, \"text\": \"\\\"Sinogene\\\", the company behind the research, says the puppies could be a medical breakthrough.\"}, {\"start\": 208.72, \"end\": 215.36, \"text\": \"The puppies are genetically designed with medical disorders in the hope of finding a\"}, {\"start\": 215.36, \"end\": 229.52, \"text\": \"cure that one day could save human lives.\"}, {\"start\": 229.68, \"end\": 239.68, \"text\": \"The original dog was genetically edited to have problems regulating cholesterol.\"}, {\"start\": 239.68, \"end\": 247.2, \"text\": \"His clones, the other three puppies, therefore have the same problem.\"}, {\"start\": 247.36, \"end\": 260.72, \"text\": \"And one dog has developed atherosclerosis, a disease that can lead to heart attack and\"}, {\"start\": 260.72, \"end\": 263.6, \"text\": \"stroke.\"}, {\"start\": 263.6, \"end\": 271.84, \"text\": \"Their whole lives will now be one test after another devoted to learning about that illness\"}, {\"start\": 271.84, \"end\": 273.84, \"text\": \"and how to treat it.\"}, {\"start\": 273.84, \"end\": 278.4, \"text\": \"But many people are questioning the ethics of the science.\"}, {\"start\": 278.4, \"end\": 281.2, \"text\": \"These dogs will not lead normal lives.\"}, {\"start\": 281.2, \"end\": 283.84, \"text\": \"They will be kept in a small room.\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 292.88, \"text\": \"Their surrogate mothers are kept in cages and not often allowed to leave.\"}, {\"start\": 292.96, \"end\": 300.64, \"text\": \"The dogs will likely become sick and could die prematurely because they were cloned for\"}, {\"start\": 300.64, \"end\": 308.8, \"text\": \"one main reason: medical research.\"}, {\"start\": 311.2, \"end\": 313.68, \"text\": \"A 500-year-old mystery at the Vatican has just been solved.\"}, {\"start\": 313.68, \"end\": 326.96, \"text\": \"The Renaissance painter, Raphael, painted famous pieces in three rooms at the Vatican.\"}, {\"start\": 327.04, \"end\": 334.96, \"text\": \"He began work on another room before his death but those paintings had never been found\"}, {\"start\": 334.96, \"end\": 337.92, \"text\": \"until now.\"}, {\"start\": 337.92, \"end\": 343.6, \"text\": \"Raphael planned to paint the whole wall in oil but died before he could finish and the\"}, {\"start\": 343.6, \"end\": 354.96, \"text\": \"figures were lost for centuries.\"}, {\"start\": 354.96, \"end\": 357.6, \"text\": \"Recently workers began cleaning the walls at the Vatican.\"}, {\"start\": 357.6, \"end\": 371.52, \"text\": \"And they discovered two paintings that depict the female figures \\\"Justice\\\" and \\\"Friendship.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 371.76, \"end\": 376.56, \"text\": \"The head of the Vatican Museums says it will take at least five years to fully restore\"}, {\"start\": 376.56, \"end\": 382.16, \"text\": \"the paintings in the room.\"}, {\"start\": 384.88, \"end\": 397.2, \"text\": \"Playing video games too much and too often will soon be recognized as a mental health\"}, {\"start\": 397.28, \"end\": 400.88, \"text\": \"disorder.\"}, {\"start\": 400.88, \"end\": 410.72, \"text\": \"\\\"Gaming Disorder\\\" will be added to the official list of diseases by the World Health Organization\"}, {\"start\": 410.72, \"end\": 413.6, \"text\": \"next year.\"}, {\"start\": 413.6, \"end\": 434.24, \"text\": \"Its symptoms include the inability to control when and how to play video games.\"}, {\"start\": 434.24, \"end\": 441.28, \"text\": \"Another red flag is when someone chooses games over other interest in life and keeps playing\"}, {\"start\": 441.28, \"end\": 446.32, \"text\": \"despite negative consequences.\"}, {\"start\": 446.32, \"end\": 453.28, \"text\": \"Experts say playing video games in itself is not a problem.\"}, {\"start\": 453.44, \"end\": 467.52, \"text\": \"It all depends on where, why and how much someone plays.\"}, {\"start\": 467.76, \"end\": 476.24, \"text\": \"Adding \\\"gaming disorder\\\" to the list means that it will be recognized by doctors and\"}, {\"start\": 476.24, \"end\": 483.04, \"text\": \"insurance companies.\"}, {\"start\": 485.6, \"end\": 490.32, \"text\": \"Yesterday was the season for giving.\"}, {\"start\": 490.32, \"end\": 493.6, \"text\": \"Today is the season for returning.\"}, {\"start\": 493.6, \"end\": 502.48, \"text\": \"Retail experts say don't feel bad if you want to return a gift you don't like or want.\"}, {\"start\": 502.56, \"end\": 510.64, \"text\": \"According to the National Retail Federation nearly 2/3 of holiday shoppers will return\"}, {\"start\": 510.64, \"end\": 515.04, \"text\": \"at least one item this year.\"}, {\"start\": 515.04, \"end\": 520.88, \"text\": \"Here are some helpful tips on how to return an item:\"}, {\"start\": 520.88, \"end\": 523.2, \"text\": \"Do it quickly.\"}, {\"start\": 523.2, \"end\": 528.72, \"text\": \"Some stores have about a two week window for returns.\"}, {\"start\": 528.88, \"end\": 534.8, \"text\": \"No matter where your gift came from, if you don't want to give it back, don't open the\"}, {\"start\": 534.8, \"end\": 537.12, \"text\": \"box.\"}, {\"start\": 537.12, \"end\": 547.44, \"text\": \"Many stores take a restocking fee out of the refund amount.\"}, {\"start\": 547.68, \"end\": 554.24, \"text\": \"Keep gift receipts and try not to remove price tags.\"}, {\"start\": 554.24, \"end\": 557.36, \"text\": \"Also bring your ID.\"}, {\"start\": 557.36, \"end\": 563.76, \"text\": \"Some stores will scan your license to prevent fraud.\"}, {\"start\": 563.76, \"end\": 571.28, \"text\": \"If your gift came in the mail, check to see if you can return in-store, which may save\"}, {\"start\": 571.52, \"end\": 577.84, \"text\": \"you money at the post office.\"}, {\"start\": 580.64, \"end\": 592.48, \"text\": \"Two young men in South Dakota find out they are more than just good friends.\"}, {\"start\": 592.48, \"end\": 595.28, \"text\": \"They are actually brothers!\"}, {\"start\": 595.28, \"end\": 608.32, \"text\": \"Omi and TJ met at a non-profit ranch that helps troubled boys.\"}, {\"start\": 608.32, \"end\": 615.04, \"text\": \"Both love horses and both have been adopted by two different families.\"}, {\"start\": 615.04, \"end\": 624.96, \"text\": \"But somehow they knew their bond was stronger than just friends.\"}, {\"start\": 624.96, \"end\": 635.36, \"text\": \"Then TJ learned that Omi's last name was Smith, which was his biological father's last name.\"}, {\"start\": 635.36, \"end\": 642.56, \"text\": \"Later they learned their mothers had the same name too.\"}, {\"start\": 642.56, \"end\": 649.44, \"text\": \"The boys went to the staff at the ranch with their suspicions.\"}, {\"start\": 649.44, \"end\": 651.84, \"text\": \"And surprise!\"}, {\"start\": 651.84, \"end\": 657.44, \"text\": \"They share both parents with 99.9% certainty.\"}, {\"start\": 657.44, \"end\": 664.8, \"text\": \"Officials at the ranch say it's a miracle they were able to connect the two brothers.\"}, {\"start\": 666.4, \"end\": 668.4, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 668.4, \"end\": 669.6, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 669.6, \"end\": 671.92, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 671.92, \"end\": 676.4, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 676.4, \"end\": 681.44, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "I_LAYEn9--A": {
    "video_id": "I_LAYEn9--A",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.16.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180217",
    "duration": 605,
    "view_count": 701,
    "description": "2.16.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Remembering the victims of the Florida school shooting    \n-FBI says it didn’t act on tip about Florida shooter        \n-Supreme court to meet Friday on DACA                      \n-McDonald’s changes Happy Meal options                                           \n-\"Black Panther” tickets sell out fast                     \n-The magic of movie make-up                                \n-Brick-to",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.06, \"end\": 9.1, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.1, \"end\": 10.98, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.98, \"end\": 12.32, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.32, \"end\": 15.5, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.34, \"end\": 26.68, \"text\": \"Seventeen students and teachers were killed in Wednesday's massacre at Marjory Stoneman\"}, {\"start\": 26.68, \"end\": 30.74, \"text\": \"Douglas high school.\"}, {\"start\": 30.74, \"end\": 41.78, \"text\": \"Mourners say their names and stories are the most important thing to come out of this tragedy\"}, {\"start\": 41.78, \"end\": 49.6, \"text\": \"and they want them all to be remember as young people who had big dreams, bright futures\"}, {\"start\": 49.6, \"end\": 52.58, \"text\": \"and were loved by so many people.\"}, {\"start\": 52.58, \"end\": 60.46, \"text\": \"They were athletes, volunteers in their community, some headed for college and one young man\"}, {\"start\": 60.46, \"end\": 63.62, \"text\": \"had just become a US citizen.\"}, {\"start\": 63.62, \"end\": 71.36, \"text\": \"Among the teachers that were killed -- one was in Iraq war veteran, one was a camp counselor\"}, {\"start\": 71.42, \"end\": 78.36, \"text\": \"and one stood by his student as he was going through cancer treatments.\"}, {\"start\": 78.36, \"end\": 89.78, \"text\": \"And they will be remembered as heroes for sacrificing their own lives by shielding students\"}, {\"start\": 89.78, \"end\": 92.12, \"text\": \"from the bullets.\"}, {\"start\": 95.38, \"end\": 101.26, \"text\": \"The FBI confirms the agency was tipped off about Florida school shooter Nikolas Cruz\"}, {\"start\": 101.26, \"end\": 102.82, \"text\": \"last month.\"}, {\"start\": 102.82, \"end\": 116.74, \"text\": \"A caller provided information on January 5th about Cruz's gun ownership, his desire to\"}, {\"start\": 116.74, \"end\": 123.06, \"text\": \"kill people, his erratic behavior and his disturbing social media posts, as well as\"}, {\"start\": 123.06, \"end\": 129.92, \"text\": \"the potential of him conducting a school shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 129.92, \"end\": 138.24, \"text\": \"The bureau said the information should have been assessed as a potential threat to life.\"}, {\"start\": 138.24, \"end\": 146.68, \"text\": \"The Miami field office never received information about the tip so an investigation was not opened.\"}, {\"start\": 149.98, \"end\": 162.84, \"text\": \"The Supreme Court met behind closed doors Friday to address an order temporarily blocking\"}, {\"start\": 162.84, \"end\": 166.32, \"text\": \"President Trump's effort to end DACA.\"}, {\"start\": 166.32, \"end\": 173.5, \"text\": \"The Justice Department is taking the rare step of asking the Supreme Court to review\"}, {\"start\": 173.5, \"end\": 177.66, \"text\": \"the decision, even before a federal appeals court has had a chance to weigh in.\"}, {\"start\": 177.66, \"end\": 187.02, \"text\": \"Under normal circumstances, the Supreme Court disapproves of parties bypassing lower court\"}, {\"start\": 187.02, \"end\": 190.8, \"text\": \"proceedings and asking for a direct review by the Supreme Court.\"}, {\"start\": 190.8, \"end\": 199.38, \"text\": \"But the fate of DACA and its roughly 700,000 participants is the subject of heated negotiations\"}, {\"start\": 199.38, \"end\": 202.58, \"text\": \"in Washington.\"}, {\"start\": 202.58, \"end\": 213.06, \"text\": \"Lawmakers are desperately searching for a way to allow the young undocumented immigrants\"}, {\"start\": 213.06, \"end\": 220.32, \"text\": \"to stay in the country while also addressing border security concerns.\"}, {\"start\": 223.88, \"end\": 233.58, \"text\": \"Say goodbye to McDonald's cheeseburger happy meal.\"}, {\"start\": 233.58, \"end\": 241.6, \"text\": \"On Thursday the fast food giant announced it will offer more balanced meals, simplify\"}, {\"start\": 241.6, \"end\": 248.32, \"text\": \"ingredients and continue to be transparent with happy meal nutrition information.\"}, {\"start\": 248.32, \"end\": 255.26, \"text\": \"As part of the plan, cheeseburgers will only be available if requested by the customer\"}, {\"start\": 255.26, \"end\": 263.44, \"text\": \"and the small sized french fries will be replaced with kid -sized fries in the 6-piece chicken\"}, {\"start\": 263.44, \"end\": 264.88, \"text\": \"McNugget meal.\"}, {\"start\": 264.88, \"end\": 270.84, \"text\": \"Bottled water will be added as a featured beverage choice as well as a reformulated\"}, {\"start\": 270.84, \"end\": 276.76, \"text\": \"chocolate milk with reduced sugar, also available only by request.\"}, {\"start\": 276.76, \"end\": 285.1, \"text\": \"By June the happy meal combinations will be 600 calories or less, making them compliant\"}, {\"start\": 285.1, \"end\": 294.98, \"text\": \"with new nutrition criteria for added sugar and saturated fat.\"}, {\"start\": 298.74, \"end\": 309.08, \"text\": \"The much-anticipated movie \\\"Black Panther\\\" hits theaters today.\"}, {\"start\": 309.08, \"end\": 312.6, \"text\": \"And tickets have already sold out around the country.\"}, {\"start\": 312.6, \"end\": 320.94, \"text\": \"It's the first Marvel superhero movie with a mostly black cast.\"}, {\"start\": 320.94, \"end\": 330.02, \"text\": \"The character was created by Stan Lee and Jack Kirby in the 1960s against the backdrop\"}, {\"start\": 330.02, \"end\": 335.38, \"text\": \"of the civil rights movement.\"}, {\"start\": 335.38, \"end\": 343.8, \"text\": \"The movie has already set a Marvel record for online presales and the experts estimate\"}, {\"start\": 343.8, \"end\": 353.92, \"text\": \"the movie will rake in anywhere from 165 million to 180 million dollars or more over the weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 353.92, \"end\": 361.38, \"text\": \"If that happens, it would set a record for a February movie debut.\"}, {\"start\": 364.78, \"end\": 388.98, \"text\": \"Sculptor Kazuhiro Tsuji shows us how he transformed actor Gary Oldman into Winston Churchill for\"}, {\"start\": 388.98, \"end\": 392.94, \"text\": \"the movie \\\"The Darkest Hour.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 392.94, \"end\": 396.38, \"text\": \"Kazu, as he is known, is a sculptor of hyper-realist faces.\"}, {\"start\": 396.38, \"end\": 408.56, \"text\": \"He likes to re-create historical figures -- the bigger, the better.\"}, {\"start\": 408.56, \"end\": 423.92, \"text\": \"He created the makeup for Jim Carrey in \\\"How The Grinch Stole Christmas.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 423.92, \"end\": 433.3, \"text\": \"And for Brad Pitt in \\\"The Curious Case of Benjamin\"}, {\"start\": 433.3, \"end\": 436.08, \"text\": \"Button.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 436.08, \"end\": 443.28, \"text\": \"But in 2012, he decided to leave the movie industry due to stress.\"}, {\"start\": 443.4, \"end\": 452.86, \"text\": \"Gary Oldman had to coax Kazu back just for this one movie.\"}, {\"start\": 452.87, \"end\": 462.55, \"text\": \"Kazu had never done a historical figure, so he agreed.\"}, {\"start\": 462.55, \"end\": 474.06, \"text\": \"He shaved Oldman's head and poured liquefied resin over it to create a molded cast.\"}, {\"start\": 474.06, \"end\": 483.96, \"text\": \"From there he began to design the prosthetics for the cheeks, nose, chin and even Adam's\"}, {\"start\": 483.96, \"end\": 485.98, \"text\": \"apple.\"}, {\"start\": 485.98, \"end\": 497.14, \"text\": \"And he made a series of wigs from baby hair and angora rabbit fur.\"}, {\"start\": 497.14, \"end\": 508.62, \"text\": \"The transformation process took more than three hours every day for 48 consecutive shooting days.\"}, {\"start\": 512.56, \"end\": 520.88, \"text\": \"Police in Shanghai released a video to show what happens when a break-in attempt goes\"}, {\"start\": 520.88, \"end\": 524.4, \"text\": \"hilariously wrong.\"}, {\"start\": 524.4, \"end\": 530.36, \"text\": \"Two suspects approach a business in the middle of the night.\"}, {\"start\": 530.36, \"end\": 534.34, \"text\": \"Each one of them has what appears to be a brick in their hands.\"}, {\"start\": 534.34, \"end\": 538.0, \"text\": \"One man throws his brick.\"}, {\"start\": 538.0, \"end\": 543.18, \"text\": \"But the second man mistimed his throw, hit his accomplice in the head and knocked him\"}, {\"start\": 543.18, \"end\": 545.52, \"text\": \"out cold.\"}, {\"start\": 545.52, \"end\": 550.22, \"text\": \"He then has a whole new problem on his hands -- trying to flee the scene while dragging\"}, {\"start\": 550.22, \"end\": 551.94, \"text\": \"his unconscious partner with him.\"}, {\"start\": 552.0, \"end\": 553.16, \"text\": \"You have to see it for yourself.\"}, {\"start\": 581.82, \"end\": 583.94, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 583.94, \"end\": 585.16, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 585.16, \"end\": 586.94, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 586.94, \"end\": 591.52, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 591.52, \"end\": 597.12, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "1wFZjYCc-8U": {
    "video_id": "1wFZjYCc-8U",
    "title": "Home Depot giving workers $1K bonuses (ASL - 1.25.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180126",
    "duration": 41,
    "view_count": 343,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.66, \"end\": 5.94, \"text\": \"Home Depot is paying $1,000 bonuses to its hourly employees.\"}, {\"start\": 5.94, \"end\": 14.96, \"text\": \"Home Depot says they are able to do this because of the recent tax reform.\"}, {\"start\": 14.96, \"end\": 17.5, \"text\": \"The bonus amounts will be based on how long the employee has worked for the company.\"}, {\"start\": 17.5, \"end\": 22.68, \"text\": \"All of Home Depot’s hourly employees will get at least $200.\"}, {\"start\": 22.68, \"end\": 27.22, \"text\": \"The maximum payout is $1,000 for employees that have worked for the company for 20 years\"}, {\"start\": 27.22, \"end\": 28.34, \"text\": \"or more.\"}, {\"start\": 28.34, \"end\": 40.22, \"text\": \"Other companies giving their employees bonuses include Disney, Starbucks and Walmart.\"}]"
  },
  "8Z2qKJWlAgY": {
    "video_id": "8Z2qKJWlAgY",
    "title": "5.27.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180528",
    "duration": 534,
    "view_count": 1227,
    "description": "5.27.18 - \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-State of emergencies in Mississippi, Florida, Alabama\n-Hero teacher in school shooting out of hospital\n-“Sesame Street” sues makers of raunchy puppet movie\n-President George H.W. Bush back n hospital\n-Trump meets with freed American prisoner\n-31st Annual Rolling Thunder Memorial Ride\n-NASA camera melts capturing SpaceX launch\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizati",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.96, \"end\": 9.08, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.08, \"end\": 11.4, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.4, \"end\": 13.02, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 13.02, \"end\": 16.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.58, \"end\": 30.08, \"text\": \"The governors in Florida, Mississippi and Alabama have all declared emergencies in their states.\"}, {\"start\": 30.08, \"end\": 41.72, \"text\": \"It's because subtropical storm Alberto continues to churn north through the Gulf of Mexico\"}, {\"start\": 41.72, \"end\": 44.82, \"text\": \"and it's gaining strength.\"}, {\"start\": 44.82, \"end\": 52.1, \"text\": \"Alberto is scheduled to make landfall on the Florida Panhandle early Monday and the three\"}, {\"start\": 52.1, \"end\": 53.72, \"text\": \"states are preparing to take the hit.\"}, {\"start\": 53.72, \"end\": 56.34, \"text\": \"The storm is expected to produce heavy rainfall, flooding and gusty winds.\"}, {\"start\": 56.34, \"end\": 60.4, \"text\": \"And that could cause dangerouw storm surges for areas along the central and eastern Gulf Coast.\"}, {\"start\": 60.4, \"end\": 66.0, \"text\": \"People living in New Orleans are being asked to get prepared and keep up with weather updates\"}, {\"start\": 66.0, \"end\": 68.64, \"text\": \"just in case.\"}, {\"start\": 70.32, \"end\": 88.52, \"text\": \"Science teacher Jason Seaman is credited with disarming a school shooter in Noblesville,\"}, {\"start\": 88.52, \"end\": 91.88, \"text\": \"Indiana last Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 91.88, \"end\": 95.96, \"text\": \"The 29-year-old was shot three times, in the abdomen, hip and forearm, while tackling and\"}, {\"start\": 95.96, \"end\": 97.2, \"text\": \"stopping the shooter.\"}, {\"start\": 97.2, \"end\": 103.84, \"text\": \"Today Seaman was released from the hospital.\"}, {\"start\": 103.84, \"end\": 106.76, \"text\": \"Two others were wounded in the shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 106.76, \"end\": 110.44, \"text\": \"One female student is in critical condition.\"}, {\"start\": 110.44, \"end\": 114.52, \"text\": \"Another student fractured his ankle.\"}, {\"start\": 114.52, \"end\": 119.88, \"text\": \"The suspect gunman, also a student, is now in custody.\"}, {\"start\": 119.88, \"end\": 127.96, \"text\": \"President Trump praised Seaman's action Saturday, calling him \\\"very brave\\\" and \\\"hero\\\" for saving\"}, {\"start\": 127.96, \"end\": 132.0, \"text\": \"so many precious lives.\"}, {\"start\": 134.48, \"end\": 144.32, \"text\": \"Actress Melissa McCarthy has a new movie coming out.\"}, {\"start\": 144.32, \"end\": 149.52, \"text\": \"It's entitled \\\"Happytime Murders.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 149.52, \"end\": 158.72, \"text\": \"It's rated R because it features puppets cursing, using drugs and having sex.\"}, {\"start\": 158.72, \"end\": 166.12, \"text\": \"The company behind Sesame Street is suing the maker of the movie but not because of\"}, {\"start\": 166.12, \"end\": 167.9, \"text\": \"the raunchy puppet scenes.\"}, {\"start\": 167.9, \"end\": 170.66, \"text\": \"The film's marketing campaign is\"}, {\"start\": 170.66, \"end\": 176.38, \"text\": \"\\\"No Sesame, All Street.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 176.38, \"end\": 185.9, \"text\": \"The lawsuit says the movie does not have the right to use the words Sesame Street in its\"}, {\"start\": 185.9, \"end\": 196.48, \"text\": \"tagline and it confuses consumers into thinking Sesame Street is associated with and endorses\"}, {\"start\": 196.48, \"end\": 201.22, \"text\": \"the movie.\"}, {\"start\": 201.22, \"end\": 218.94, \"text\": \"The lawsuit is asking for a jury trial, punitive damages\"}, {\"start\": 218.94, \"end\": 222.06, \"text\": \"and that the movie change its advertising.\"}, {\"start\": 222.06, \"end\": 226.6, \"text\": \"The movie hits theaters on August 17.\"}, {\"start\": 229.72, \"end\": 238.28, \"text\": \"Former President George H.W. Bush is back in the hospital.\"}, {\"start\": 238.28, \"end\": 242.88, \"text\": \"According to a spokesperson, he was taken to a Maine facility after experiencing low\"}, {\"start\": 242.88, \"end\": 248.72, \"text\": \"blood pressure and fatigue.\"}, {\"start\": 248.72, \"end\": 254.92, \"text\": \"He is expected to stay there for a few days for observation.\"}, {\"start\": 254.92, \"end\": 261.92, \"text\": \"The hospital stay comes a day after Bush visited with veterans at a Memorial Day event in\"}, {\"start\": 261.92, \"end\": 265.12, \"text\": \"Kennebunkport, Maine.\"}, {\"start\": 265.12, \"end\": 276.36, \"text\": \"He chatted and took pictures with veterans from World War II, Korea, Vietnam, Iraq and\"}, {\"start\": 276.36, \"end\": 282.9, \"text\": \"Afghanistan.\"}, {\"start\": 282.9, \"end\": 295.76, \"text\": \"Last month, Bush was hospitalized for an infection the day after the funeral for his wife, Barbara Bush.\"}, {\"start\": 297.52, \"end\": 313.6, \"text\": \"American missionary Josh Holt is back on US soil after being released from a Venezuelan prison.\"}, {\"start\": 313.6, \"end\": 318.98, \"text\": \"One of his first stops was the White House, where he met with President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 318.98, \"end\": 324.74, \"text\": \"Holt said he was overwhelmed with gratitude and thanked everyone for their support.\"}, {\"start\": 324.76, \"end\": 333.46, \"text\": \"In 2016 Holt traveled to Venezuela to marry his fiancee but was arrested shortly afterward.\"}, {\"start\": 333.46, \"end\": 343.94, \"text\": \"He was accused by the Venezuelan government of stockpiling weapons and trying to destabilize\"}, {\"start\": 343.94, \"end\": 347.16, \"text\": \"the government.\"}, {\"start\": 347.16, \"end\": 352.88, \"text\": \"He was held for nearly 2 years without standing trial.\"}, {\"start\": 353.92, \"end\": 363.04, \"text\": \"Thousands of bikers from across the country were in the nation's capital for the \\\"Rolling\"}, {\"start\": 363.04, \"end\": 366.86, \"text\": \"Thunder\\\" rally.\"}, {\"start\": 366.86, \"end\": 374.82, \"text\": \"It is a Memorial Day tradition that pays tribute to military veterans and those who gave their\"}, {\"start\": 374.82, \"end\": 377.88, \"text\": \"lives in service.\"}, {\"start\": 377.88, \"end\": 390.68, \"text\": \"The ride started at the Pentagon then through the National Mall to the Lincoln and Vietnam\"}, {\"start\": 390.68, \"end\": 392.86, \"text\": \"memorials.\"}, {\"start\": 392.86, \"end\": 402.14, \"text\": \"The event included speeches, performances and a Memorial Day concert Sunday evening.\"}, {\"start\": 402.14, \"end\": 410.88, \"text\": \"\\\"Rolling Thunder\\\" started in 1987 to call attention to any prisoners of war or those\"}, {\"start\": 410.88, \"end\": 415.24, \"text\": \"listed as missing in action.\"}, {\"start\": 415.24, \"end\": 426.16, \"text\": \"Many of the bikes fly American flags or the black-and-white POW-MIA flag.\"}, {\"start\": 426.16, \"end\": 433.24, \"text\": \"Riders say they are also committed to helping US veterans from all wars.\"}, {\"start\": 435.56, \"end\": 446.74, \"text\": \"We have new pictures from NASA showing a camera getting toasted during a SpaceX launch.\"}, {\"start\": 446.74, \"end\": 456.84, \"text\": \"A NASA photographer set up a bunch of cameras to capture last week's launch from Vandenberg\"}, {\"start\": 456.84, \"end\": 461.26, \"text\": \"Air Force Base in California.\"}, {\"start\": 461.26, \"end\": 466.56, \"text\": \"The launch started a brush fire which overtakes and melts the camera.\"}, {\"start\": 466.56, \"end\": 472.64, \"text\": \"But the camera kept taking pictures until the very end.\"}, {\"start\": 472.64, \"end\": 473.46, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 481.12, \"end\": 491.26, \"text\": \"The camera was completely charred but the memory card was still intact.\"}, {\"start\": 491.3, \"end\": 501.86, \"text\": \"And interestingly enough, it was farthest away, about a quarter of a mile from the launch site.\"}, {\"start\": 504.2, \"end\": 506.86, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 506.86, \"end\": 508.16, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 508.16, \"end\": 511.96, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 511.96, \"end\": 517.84, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 517.92, \"end\": 520.6, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 520.6, \"end\": 522.24, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 522.24, \"end\": 525.8, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "3Uhjd1gWESY": {
    "video_id": "3Uhjd1gWESY",
    "title": "\"March for our lives\" rallies around the world (ASL - 3.24.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180325",
    "duration": 54,
    "view_count": 115,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.56, \"end\": 6.92, \"text\": \"Millions of protesters around the country and the world came together for the massive\"}, {\"start\": 6.92, \"end\": 10.22, \"text\": \"\\\"March For Our Lives\\\" demonstrations Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 10.22, \"end\": 17.06, \"text\": \"This is a map of the 800+ rallies taking place across America.\"}, {\"start\": 17.06, \"end\": 26.0, \"text\": \"The event was organized by survivors of the school shooting that left 17 people dead in\"}, {\"start\": 26.0, \"end\": 29.04, \"text\": \"Parkland, Florida last month.\"}, {\"start\": 29.04, \"end\": 34.0, \"text\": \"The demonstrators say they were tired of hearing politicians say \\\"Our thoughts and prayers\"}, {\"start\": 34.0, \"end\": 36.2, \"text\": \"are with you.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 36.2, \"end\": 45.04, \"text\": \"They are demanding action, calling for stricter gun control laws and safer schools.\"}, {\"start\": 45.04, \"end\": 53.2, \"text\": \"Celebrities became advocates, teachers became activists and parents became protesters.\"}]"
  },
  "8A3jpDQmkPA": {
    "video_id": "8A3jpDQmkPA",
    "title": "5.16.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180517",
    "duration": 444,
    "view_count": 996,
    "description": "5.16.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Trump Tower transcripts released\n-Rapper T.I. arrested\n-Senate votes to repeal changes to net neutrality\n-Family reunited after 31 years\n-Smithsonian unveils portrait of Henrietta Lacks\n-Scientists train spider to jump on command!\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.72, \"end\": 9.42, \"text\": \"Hello everyone!\"}, {\"start\": 9.42, \"end\": 10.82, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.82, \"end\": 12.74, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.74, \"end\": 15.58, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for the day.\"}, {\"start\": 18.22, \"end\": 26.12, \"text\": \"In 2016 Donald Trump Junior met with the Russians at the Trump Tower.\"}, {\"start\": 26.12, \"end\": 36.66, \"text\": \"Nearly 2,000 pages of transcripts were released today by the Senate Judiciary Committee.\"}, {\"start\": 36.66, \"end\": 47.96, \"text\": \"In those transcripts are details of a 2016 meeting Donald Trump Junior had with others in New York.\"}, {\"start\": 47.96, \"end\": 59.12, \"text\": \"And details of how Donald Trump Junior, Trump's son-in-law, Jerry Kushner and former campaign\"}, {\"start\": 59.12, \"end\": 74.38, \"text\": \"chairman Paul Manafort were expecting dirt on Hillary Clinton from a Russia lawyer.\"}, {\"start\": 74.38, \"end\": 81.28, \"text\": \"The meeting and whether President Trump knew about it is the focus of special counsel Robert\"}, {\"start\": 81.28, \"end\": 90.44, \"text\": \"Mueller's investigation into Russian meddling in the 2016 election.\"}, {\"start\": 90.44, \"end\": 98.48, \"text\": \"In the transcripts Donald Junior told congressional investigators he was interested in listening\"}, {\"start\": 98.48, \"end\": 103.72, \"text\": \"to information from a Russia lawyer that could damage Clinton's campaign.\"}, {\"start\": 103.72, \"end\": 108.76, \"text\": \"He said he did not discuss this with his father.\"}, {\"start\": 110.0, \"end\": 119.66, \"text\": \"The lawyer for rapper TI released a statement today.\"}, {\"start\": 119.66, \"end\": 123.48, \"text\": \"TI, whose real name is Clifford Harris, Junior, was arrested outside of the\"}, {\"start\": 123.48, \"end\": 126.48, \"text\": \"gated community where he lives in Atlanta, Georgia.\"}, {\"start\": 126.48, \"end\": 134.08, \"text\": \"His attorney says Harris forgot his keys and went to the guard shack.\"}, {\"start\": 134.08, \"end\": 139.4, \"text\": \"He woke up the guard, who was sleeping, for entry into the gate but the guard refused to let him in.\"}, {\"start\": 139.4, \"end\": 147.0, \"text\": \"Harris even called his wife who was inside the couple's home but the guard still would not\"}, {\"start\": 147.0, \"end\": 149.84, \"text\": \"let him through the gate.\"}, {\"start\": 149.84, \"end\": 158.8, \"text\": \"The statement reports \\\"words were exchanged\\\" and the guard or supervisor called the police.\"}, {\"start\": 158.8, \"end\": 169.2, \"text\": \"The Henry County Sheriff's Office says Harris was cited on misdemeanor charges of simple assault,\"}, {\"start\": 169.2, \"end\": 172.72, \"text\": \"disorderly conduct and public drunkeness.\"}, {\"start\": 172.72, \"end\": 176.32, \"text\": \"Harris is out on bond.\"}, {\"start\": 178.8, \"end\": 184.08, \"text\": \"The Senate voted to pass a bill that would repeal changes to net neutrality recently\"}, {\"start\": 184.08, \"end\": 185.52, \"text\": \"passed by the FCC.\"}, {\"start\": 185.52, \"end\": 192.08, \"text\": \"Net neutrality prohibited internet service providers from speeding up or slowing down\"}, {\"start\": 192.08, \"end\": 196.96, \"text\": \"traffic from specific websites and apps.\"}, {\"start\": 196.96, \"end\": 202.2, \"text\": \"The FCC voted in December to repeal Obama-era protections including neutrality.\"}, {\"start\": 202.2, \"end\": 212.84, \"text\": \"Today, the senate passed a bill to keep net neutrality fair for everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 212.84, \"end\": 217.16, \"text\": \"The bill was backed up by Democrat and Republican senators.\"}, {\"start\": 217.16, \"end\": 223.24, \"text\": \"Democrats used the Congressional Review Act to force a vote.\"}, {\"start\": 224.48, \"end\": 229.44, \"text\": \"A tearful reunion for a family in China.\"}, {\"start\": 229.44, \"end\": 238.4, \"text\": \"It was the first time in 31-years that Yang Shenghua and his wife have seen their son.\"}, {\"start\": 238.4, \"end\": 244.68, \"text\": \"Their son was two-years-old he went missing at a train station.\"}, {\"start\": 244.68, \"end\": 249.8, \"text\": \"The couple spent years searching for him.\"}, {\"start\": 249.8, \"end\": 254.88, \"text\": \"In 2011, they gave police their DNA to help in the search.\"}, {\"start\": 254.88, \"end\": 257.8, \"text\": \"Seven years later there was a match.\"}, {\"start\": 257.8, \"end\": 262.2, \"text\": \"Their son lived only about six miles away.\"}, {\"start\": 262.2, \"end\": 267.56, \"text\": \"He moved in the home two months after he went missing.\"}, {\"start\": 267.56, \"end\": 271.88, \"text\": \"He was raised by another couple who gave him a new name.\"}, {\"start\": 271.88, \"end\": 278.8, \"text\": \"No word on how he was brought in by that family or if that couple will face any charges.\"}, {\"start\": 281.32, \"end\": 289.28, \"text\": \"The Smithsonian unveiled a portrait of Henrietta Lacks in Washington, D.C.\"}, {\"start\": 289.28, \"end\": 300.76, \"text\": \"Lacks was a black tobacco farmer who died in 1951 from an aggressive form of cervical cancer.\"}, {\"start\": 300.76, \"end\": 308.48, \"text\": \"During her treatment a surgeon harvested her cells without her consent.\"}, {\"start\": 308.48, \"end\": 317.72, \"text\": \"Those cells became the first human cell line to successfully reproduce outside of the body.\"}, {\"start\": 317.72, \"end\": 321.92, \"text\": \"Scientists called them HE-LA cells.\"}, {\"start\": 321.92, \"end\": 334.56, \"text\": \"Those cells allowed advances in cancer treatments, AIDS research, cloning, stem-cell studies\"}, {\"start\": 334.56, \"end\": 335.72, \"text\": \"and much more.\"}, {\"start\": 335.72, \"end\": 338.64, \"text\": \"The portrait will hang inside one of the main entrances of the National Portrait Gallery.\"}, {\"start\": 348.96, \"end\": 351.04, \"text\": \"The portrait hang inside through November.\"}, {\"start\": 352.96, \"end\": 358.72, \"text\": \"Scientist have trained this writer to jump on command.\"}, {\"start\": 378.72, \"end\": 380.16, \"text\": \"Why would they do this?!\"}, {\"start\": 380.16, \"end\": 385.36, \"text\": \"This was a part of a study by researchers to train a spider to jump for the first time.\"}, {\"start\": 385.36, \"end\": 387.6, \"text\": \"How did they do it?\"}, {\"start\": 387.6, \"end\": 395.08, \"text\": \"Not with food because spiders only once a week.\"}, {\"start\": 395.08, \"end\": 404.14, \"text\": \"Instead, they manually moved \\\"Kim\\\" from one platform to another again and again.\"}, {\"start\": 404.14, \"end\": 408.2, \"text\": \"Eventually, Kim was trained to make the jump herself.\"}, {\"start\": 408.2, \"end\": 419.24, \"text\": \"The team said once Kim started jumping, she never missed.\"}, {\"start\": 422.24, \"end\": 424.36, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 424.36, \"end\": 425.8, \"text\": \"I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 425.8, \"end\": 427.68, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 427.68, \"end\": 431.36, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 431.36, \"end\": 432.72, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 432.72, \"end\": 433.8, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 433.8, \"end\": 436.64, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "_Abo4EGDlfo": {
    "video_id": "_Abo4EGDlfo",
    "title": "China accuses Trump of spreading “fake news” (ASL - 4.4.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180405",
    "duration": 83,
    "view_count": 227,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.9, \"end\": 13.02, \"text\": \"The world's two largest economies, China and United States, are locked in a tariff tit-for-tat.\"}, {\"start\": 13.02, \"end\": 19.94, \"text\": \"China and the United States have announced tariffs on more than $100 billion worth of\"}, {\"start\": 19.94, \"end\": 22.6, \"text\": \"combined goods.\"}, {\"start\": 22.6, \"end\": 29.94, \"text\": \"The latest clash came Wednesday when the Chinese government proposed new tariffs on dozens\"}, {\"start\": 29.94, \"end\": 36.54, \"text\": \"of US products including airplanes, cars and soybeans.\"}, {\"start\": 36.54, \"end\": 42.82, \"text\": \"President Trump downplayed the tariffs on Twitter Wednesday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 42.82, \"end\": 48.82, \"text\": \"He insists the US is not in a trade war with China.\"}, {\"start\": 48.82, \"end\": 60.04, \"text\": \"He also slammed previous US leaders who he says allowed China's theft of US intellectual\"}, {\"start\": 60.04, \"end\": 69.96, \"text\": \"property.\"}, {\"start\": 69.96, \"end\": 75.16, \"text\": \"Beijing responded to those claims by saying: \\\"As for the media reports, we think would\"}, {\"start\": 75.16, \"end\": 81.6, \"text\": \"like to use the term President Trump often loves to say and call them 'fake news.'\\\"\"}]"
  },
  "MTY9lPOvwzc": {
    "video_id": "MTY9lPOvwzc",
    "title": "Dr. G answers your questions: How many people have recovered from coronavirus?",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200321",
    "duration": 195,
    "view_count": 497,
    "description": "3.20.20",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.1, \"end\": 2.56, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 2.56, \"end\": 9.44, \"text\": \"My name is Dr. Deborah Gilboa or Dr. G.\"}, {\"start\": 9.44, \"end\": 13.22, \"text\": \"I'm a hearing family physician.\"}, {\"start\": 13.26, \"end\": 15.04, \"text\": \"My parents are hearing as well.\"}, {\"start\": 15.04, \"end\": 18.02, \"text\": \"If my signing is not clear I apologize.\"}, {\"start\": 18.16, \"end\": 26.38, \"text\": \"But right now many of my Deaf patients are asking lots of questions about coronavirus\"}, {\"start\": 26.38, \"end\": 28.64, \"text\": \"and Covid-19.\"}, {\"start\": 28.64, \"end\": 33.82, \"text\": \"They want to know what to do, what's real, how to help myself, how to protect my family\"}, {\"start\": 33.82, \"end\": 36.1, \"text\": \"and what's important.\"}, {\"start\": 36.24, \"end\": 42.84, \"text\": \"So I wanted to answer some of your questions right now.\"}, {\"start\": 45.94, \"end\": 51.5, \"text\": \"The first question is from Kaytee Kelly.\"}, {\"start\": 51.5, \"end\": 58.16, \"text\": \"She wanted to know how many people have recovered.\"}, {\"start\": 58.16, \"end\": 59.9, \"text\": \"That's a good question.\"}, {\"start\": 59.9, \"end\": 68.72, \"text\": \"At this moment 85,000 people around the world have recovered and that's good news.\"}, {\"start\": 68.72, \"end\": 70.7, \"text\": \"And we will see more.\"}, {\"start\": 70.7, \"end\": 81.28, \"text\": \"Kaytee you also said you heard that older people are at a higher risk and you want to\"}, {\"start\": 81.28, \"end\": 87.1, \"text\": \"know if children, babies and young adults are at risk as well.\"}, {\"start\": 87.16, \"end\": 89.08, \"text\": \"That's a really good question as well\"}, {\"start\": 89.08, \"end\": 91.62, \"text\": \"I want to answer that clearly.\"}, {\"start\": 91.62, \"end\": 97.7, \"text\": \"First of all the risk is high for older people above 60 year old.\"}, {\"start\": 97.7, \"end\": 102.44, \"text\": \"It's worse for people over 70 and 80.\"}, {\"start\": 102.44, \"end\": 108.02, \"text\": \"As for kids, yes kids and young adults can get sick.\"}, {\"start\": 108.08, \"end\": 111.28, \"text\": \"They are more likely to recover.\"}, {\"start\": 111.28, \"end\": 121.54, \"text\": \"But it's important to know they may seem healthy but they have breathing problems, heart problems\"}, {\"start\": 121.64, \"end\": 123.78, \"text\": \"and kidney problems.\"}, {\"start\": 123.78, \"end\": 130.06, \"text\": \"And what makes it worse if they are taking medication for cancer or other things.\"}, {\"start\": 130.06, \"end\": 132.38, \"text\": \"That makes them at a higher risk.\"}, {\"start\": 132.38, \"end\": 139.68, \"text\": \"If you look at someone, they seem healthy but really they may be at risk.\"}, {\"start\": 139.86, \"end\": 144.24, \"text\": \"So everyone must protect themselves and other people as well.\"}, {\"start\": 144.24, \"end\": 151.02, \"text\": \"Also I want you to know that the risk is high for people ages 11 to 30.\"}, {\"start\": 151.02, \"end\": 158.2, \"text\": \"They're not sick but they are carriers of the virus.\"}, {\"start\": 158.2, \"end\": 168.94, \"text\": \"That means I can touch something, catch coronavirus and not become sick.\"}, {\"start\": 168.959, \"end\": 175.349, \"text\": \"But I can still spread the virus to other people when I touch things like the shopping\"}, {\"start\": 175.349, \"end\": 181.489, \"text\": \"cart at the grocery store or the counter at the post office.\"}, {\"start\": 181.489, \"end\": 187.5, \"text\": \"Then if someone else touches those things three hours or three days later, they can\"}, {\"start\": 187.5, \"end\": 189.86, \"text\": \"catch the virus and become sick.\"}, {\"start\": 189.86, \"end\": 192.78, \"text\": \"So being at home is best.\"}, {\"start\": 192.8, \"end\": 194.92, \"text\": \"Please stay home.\"}]"
  },
  "Id3E3Myp_uQ": {
    "video_id": "Id3E3Myp_uQ",
    "title": "Zuckerberg breaks silence, addresses data scandal (ASL - 3.21.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180322",
    "duration": 138,
    "view_count": 314,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 2.32, \"end\": 17.86, \"text\": \"For the first time, we are hearing from Facebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg about a data scandal engulfing\"}, {\"start\": 17.86, \"end\": 22.12, \"text\": \"the social media giant.\"}, {\"start\": 22.12, \"end\": 33.76, \"text\": \"He posted a comment on Facebook saying the company has a responsibility to protect user data.\"}, {\"start\": 33.76, \"end\": 40.18, \"text\": \"He says Facebook will take a series of steps to fix what he called a \\\"breach of trust\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 40.18, \"end\": 44.3, \"text\": \"between Facebook and its users.\"}, {\"start\": 44.3, \"end\": 53.56, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg also says he's working to understand what exactly happened.\"}, {\"start\": 53.56, \"end\": 65.14, \"text\": \"Also today a class-action lawsuit was filed in federal court against Facebook and Cambridge\"}, {\"start\": 65.14, \"end\": 76.86, \"text\": \"Analytica for collecting the personal information of 50 million Facebook users.\"}, {\"start\": 76.86, \"end\": 82.84, \"text\": \"It was filed by a Maryland woman who says her privacy was violated when her information\"}, {\"start\": 82.84, \"end\": 87.38, \"text\": \"was disclosed without permission.\"}, {\"start\": 87.38, \"end\": 98.76, \"text\": \"The lawsuit was filed in federal court in San Jose, California, where Facebook is based.\"}, {\"start\": 98.76, \"end\": 107.18, \"text\": \"The woman says the lawsuit is for all Facebook users in the US whose personal information\"}, {\"start\": 107.18, \"end\": 117.64, \"text\": \"was obtained by Cambridge Analytica without authorization.\"}, {\"start\": 117.64, \"end\": 126.3, \"text\": \"A judge will decide whether the lawsuit will be certified as a class action.\"}, {\"start\": 126.3, \"end\": 132.74, \"text\": \"If that happens and you think your personal information was collected, we will update\"}, {\"start\": 132.74, \"end\": 136.5, \"text\": \"you on how you can become part of the class action lawsuit.\"}]"
  },
  "rmFwPc96YUY": {
    "video_id": "rmFwPc96YUY",
    "title": "Super Bowl anti-terrorism documents left on plane (ASL - 2.5.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180206",
    "duration": 151,
    "view_count": 133,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.24, \"end\": 18.04, \"text\": \"The Department of Homeland Security documents were found in the seat back pocket of a commercial\"}, {\"start\": 18.04, \"end\": 20.16, \"text\": \"airplane.\"}, {\"start\": 20.16, \"end\": 29.08, \"text\": \"Most of the documents were marked \\\"For Official Use Only.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 29.08, \"end\": 37.52, \"text\": \"The documents detailed anti-terrorism preparations for Sunday night's Super Bowl -- 78 pages\"}, {\"start\": 44.6, \"end\": 74.34, \"text\": \"containing details of preparations in the event of a biological attack.\"}, {\"start\": 74.34, \"end\": 78.88, \"text\": \"The document also spelled out specific instructions on how to safeguard the document.\"}, {\"start\": 78.88, \"end\": 87.36, \"text\": \"It said the document should be stored in a locked drawer after business hours, the contents\"}, {\"start\": 87.36, \"end\": 90.4, \"text\": \"should not be shared with individuals who do not have operational \\\"need-to-know\\\" and\"}, {\"start\": 90.4, \"end\": 99.52, \"text\": \"the document should be shredded before discarding.\"}, {\"start\": 99.52, \"end\": 108.56, \"text\": \"And the document included the travel itinerary of a senior manager at DHS, the man in charge\"}, {\"start\": 108.8, \"end\": 119.6, \"text\": \"of the government's detection and response to a bio-terror attack.\"}, {\"start\": 119.6, \"end\": 128.88, \"text\": \"CNN was unable to verify who left the documents on the plane but the travel itinerary and\"}, {\"start\": 128.88, \"end\": 139.28, \"text\": \"boarding pass accompanying the documents were in the name of Michael V. Walter.\"}, {\"start\": 139.44, \"end\": 145.52, \"text\": \"According to his LinkedIn profile, Walter is a microbiologist and has been the program\"}, {\"start\": 145.53, \"end\": 149.35, \"text\": \"manager of \\\"Bio-Watch\\\" since 2009.\"}]"
  },
  "XV5n_GN606Q": {
    "video_id": "XV5n_GN606Q",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.12.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180313",
    "duration": 372,
    "view_count": 890,
    "description": "3.12.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-NY helicopter crash moment of impact\n-Three deadly packages explode in Texas neighborhoods \n-National School Walkout Day\n-Father of FL shooting victim paints powerful mural\n-Beyonce and Jay-Z announce new tour\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal acce",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 8.92, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.92, \"end\": 11.18, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.18, \"end\": 12.78, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 12.78, \"end\": 15.98, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.68, \"end\": 24.02, \"text\": \"We have the video of the moment a chartered helicopter in New York City slowly loses altitude\"}, {\"start\": 24.02, \"end\": 26.92, \"text\": \"and crashes into the East River.\"}, {\"start\": 26.92, \"end\": 30.78, \"text\": \"The blades slice the water briefly and then the craft stinks into the frigid water.\"}, {\"start\": 44.36, \"end\": 51.98, \"text\": \"Emergency crews had trouble getting the passengers out because they were tightly harnessed and\"}, {\"start\": 51.98, \"end\": 57.52, \"text\": \"the harnesses had to be cut while the helicopter was upside down and underwater.\"}, {\"start\": 57.52, \"end\": 69.66, \"text\": \"All five passengers on board died; two are pronounced dead at the scene, three others\"}, {\"start\": 69.66, \"end\": 72.89, \"text\": \"died afterwards.\"}, {\"start\": 72.89, \"end\": 77.26, \"text\": \"The pilot was the only survivor.\"}, {\"start\": 77.26, \"end\": 84.54, \"text\": \"He told investigators he believes one of the passengers' bags may have hit the emergency\"}, {\"start\": 84.54, \"end\": 90.9, \"text\": \"fuel shut off button by mistake.\"}, {\"start\": 92.72, \"end\": 101.96, \"text\": \"Law enforcement agencies in Austin, Texas have issued an emergency public safety alert.\"}, {\"start\": 101.96, \"end\": 109.06, \"text\": \"Three package bombs have exploded over the last 10 days and investigators believe they\"}, {\"start\": 109.06, \"end\": 112.88, \"text\": \"are somehow connected.\"}, {\"start\": 112.88, \"end\": 123.76, \"text\": \"In all three incidents, the victims picked up a strange package left on their doorstep,\"}, {\"start\": 123.76, \"end\": 125.98, \"text\": \"then it exploded.\"}, {\"start\": 125.98, \"end\": 136.52, \"text\": \"The last two explosions happened this morning within hours and a few blocks of each other.\"}, {\"start\": 136.52, \"end\": 139.58, \"text\": \"The first blast happened on March 2.\"}, {\"start\": 139.64, \"end\": 141.88, \"text\": \"One person was killed.\"}, {\"start\": 141.88, \"end\": 145.16, \"text\": \"Two others were critically injured.\"}, {\"start\": 145.16, \"end\": 153.38, \"text\": \"Until the person or persons responsible is caught, police are urging residents not to\"}, {\"start\": 153.38, \"end\": 157.62, \"text\": \"touch or open any unexpected packages and to call 911 immediately.\"}, {\"start\": 159.28, \"end\": 164.06, \"text\": \"Teachers and school administrators across the country are bracing themselves for this\"}, {\"start\": 164.06, \"end\": 166.82, \"text\": \"Wednesday, March 14.\"}, {\"start\": 166.82, \"end\": 173.12, \"text\": \"That's when millions of students say they plan to participate in the National School Walkout.\"}, {\"start\": 173.32, \"end\": 178.9, \"text\": \"The walkout is both a protest and a memorial.\"}, {\"start\": 178.9, \"end\": 190.4, \"text\": \"It is scheduled for 10 AM local time and will last for 17 minutes to honor the lives of\"}, {\"start\": 190.4, \"end\": 198.78, \"text\": \"the 17 people killed at Marjory Stoneman Douglas high school last month.\"}, {\"start\": 198.78, \"end\": 207.28, \"text\": \"The walkout is also a protest to urge lawmakers to pass stricter gun control laws.\"}, {\"start\": 207.28, \"end\": 214.14, \"text\": \"Many schools are allowing their students to walk out of class to exercise their freedom\"}, {\"start\": 214.14, \"end\": 222.58, \"text\": \"of speech but others are forbidding it, claiming it will disrupt class time.\"}, {\"start\": 222.58, \"end\": 227.42, \"text\": \"If you are planning to participate in National School Walkout Day, we would love to hear\"}, {\"start\": 227.42, \"end\": 228.819, \"text\": \"your thoughts.\"}, {\"start\": 228.82, \"end\": 235.34, \"text\": \"Post a comment on our Facebook page and we will share some of your thoughts during tomorrow's\"}, {\"start\": 235.34, \"end\": 236.8, \"text\": \"show.\"}, {\"start\": 240.15, \"end\": 247.96, \"text\": \"Manuel Oliver painted this mural to honor his late son.\"}, {\"start\": 247.96, \"end\": 257.68, \"text\": \"Joaquin Oliver was among the 17 students and teachers killed in the February 14 shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 257.68, \"end\": 271.28, \"text\": \"The mural reads \\\"We Demand A Change.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 271.28, \"end\": 277.6, \"text\": \"The artwork is part of the \\\"Parkland 17\\\" exhibit, an art exhibit organized by Miami Heat player\"}, {\"start\": 277.6, \"end\": 296.3, \"text\": \"Dwayne Wade and created by Miami-area artists Evan Pestain.\"}, {\"start\": 298.22, \"end\": 305.04, \"text\": \"Beyonce and Jay-Z will be back on stage together this summer.\"}, {\"start\": 305.04, \"end\": 318.7, \"text\": \"On Monday the power couple announced their joint tour entitled \\\"On The Run Two.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 318.7, \"end\": 327.02, \"text\": \"It begins June 6 in Cardiff, United Kingdom and continues through 15 European cities before\"}, {\"start\": 327.02, \"end\": 330.3, \"text\": \"arriving in North America on July 25.\"}, {\"start\": 330.3, \"end\": 337.02, \"text\": \"Beyonce and Jay-Z last toured together in 2014.\"}, {\"start\": 337.02, \"end\": 339.52, \"text\": \"Tickets go on sale next Wednesday March 14.\"}, {\"start\": 343.16, \"end\": 346.52, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 346.52, \"end\": 348.0, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 348.0, \"end\": 351.7, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 351.7, \"end\": 357.68, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 357.68, \"end\": 362.98, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "Pwv3j_jgoSU": {
    "video_id": "Pwv3j_jgoSU",
    "title": "Deadly storms strike Western Europe (ASL - 1.19.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180120",
    "duration": 75,
    "view_count": 218,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.0, \"end\": 12.76, \"text\": \"A massive windstorm in Western Europe has killed eight people -- two in the Netherlands\"}, {\"start\": 12.76, \"end\": 18.74, \"text\": \"and six in Germany.\"}, {\"start\": 18.74, \"end\": 31.64, \"text\": \"The wind is so strong it is flipping trucks off the road, ripping roofs off buildings\"}, {\"start\": 31.64, \"end\": 35.4, \"text\": \"and pulling trees up from the roots.\"}, {\"start\": 35.4, \"end\": 37.28, \"text\": \"Here's video showing the destructive force of the wind.\"}, {\"start\": 63.62, \"end\": 72.36, \"text\": \"Conditions are so bad Amsterdam was forced to close its airport, leaving thousands of\"}, {\"start\": 72.36, \"end\": 74.34, \"text\": \"passengers stranded.\"}]"
  },
  "OsujvC5NZwM": {
    "video_id": "OsujvC5NZwM",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.6.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180307",
    "duration": 490,
    "view_count": 997,
    "description": "3.6.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-DPN 30 year anniversary\n-Nashville mayor resigns, admits to affair and theft\n-Florida gun measure passes Senate, heads to House\n-Northeast bracing for another winter storm\n-W. Virgina lawmakers agree to teacher pay raise\n-Diet talk with teens may cause weight issues later\n\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and infor",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.42, \"end\": 8.84, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.84, \"end\": 10.98, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.98, \"end\": 12.56, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.56, \"end\": 16.14, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.06, \"end\": 24.66, \"text\": \"Today marks a groundbreaking day in Deaf history and American history.\"}, {\"start\": 24.66, \"end\": 32.38, \"text\": \"Thirty years ago students at Gallaudet University kicked off a massive protest, demanding the\"}, {\"start\": 32.38, \"end\": 34.4, \"text\": \"school appoint a Deaf president.\"}, {\"start\": 34.4, \"end\": 41.9, \"text\": \"When the board hired a hearing person instead, the students became livid!\"}, {\"start\": 41.9, \"end\": 47.9, \"text\": \"What happened next was a weeklong protest that made news all around the world.\"}, {\"start\": 47.9, \"end\": 51.92, \"text\": \"\\\"Deaf President Now\\\" became the rallying cry and the protest made its way all the way to\"}, {\"start\": 51.92, \"end\": 56.04, \"text\": \"Capitol Hill.\"}, {\"start\": 56.08, \"end\": 61.82, \"text\": \"Eventually the board conceded and I. King Jordan was named Gallaudet's as first Deaf\"}, {\"start\": 61.82, \"end\": 63.34, \"text\": \"president.\"}, {\"start\": 63.34, \"end\": 73.74, \"text\": \"Two weeks ago Gallaudet's board announced an official resolution marking March 6th-13th\"}, {\"start\": 73.74, \"end\": 75.58, \"text\": \"as \\\"DPN Week.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 75.58, \"end\": 80.6, \"text\": \"Yesterday Sign1News anchor Candace Jones spoke with the four student-leaders who led the\"}, {\"start\": 80.6, \"end\": 100.24, \"text\": \"protest 30 years ago: Jerry Covell, Tim Rarus, Bridgetta Bourne and Greg Hlibok.\"}, {\"start\": 100.24, \"end\": 109.14, \"text\": \"Hlibok explains why this week is so important for the younger generation.\"}, {\"start\": 109.14, \"end\": 120.26, \"text\": \"It's important for us to recognize DPN, to celebrate and cherish it as part of our Deaf history.\"}, {\"start\": 120.3, \"end\": 131.26, \"text\": \"More and more young people don't know the history of DPN and the impact that it had.\"}, {\"start\": 131.26, \"end\": 138.7, \"text\": \"We won't be around forever so we have to passed down that history.\"}, {\"start\": 140.0, \"end\": 144.6, \"text\": \"If you missed the live interview with the DPN leaders, just head to our Facebook page\"}, {\"start\": 144.6, \"end\": 147.06, \"text\": \"and you can see it in its entirety.\"}, {\"start\": 150.46, \"end\": 158.84, \"text\": \"Today Megan Barry resigned as mayor of Nashville, Tennessee.\"}, {\"start\": 158.84, \"end\": 167.86, \"text\": \"She pleaded guilty to felony theft of property worth more than $10,000.\"}, {\"start\": 167.86, \"end\": 178.5, \"text\": \"In January she also admitted to having an affair with her personal bodyguard Rob Forrest\"}, {\"start\": 178.5, \"end\": 180.8, \"text\": \"in 2016.\"}, {\"start\": 180.8, \"end\": 183.08, \"text\": \"He also pleaded guilty to felony theft of property worth more than $10,000.\"}, {\"start\": 183.08, \"end\": 188.75, \"text\": \"Both have agreed to repay the money and serve three years probation.\"}, {\"start\": 188.75, \"end\": 196.24, \"text\": \"It's not clear if today's guilty pleas are related to the affair but a local newspaper\"}, {\"start\": 196.24, \"end\": 205.64, \"text\": \"did discover in 2017 Barry and Forest traveled all over the world together for work and Forrest\"}, {\"start\": 205.64, \"end\": 209.06, \"text\": \"racked up $83,000 in expenses and overtime.\"}, {\"start\": 209.06, \"end\": 215.54, \"text\": \"Authorities also discovered nude cell phone pictures which may indicate Forrest was having\"}, {\"start\": 215.54, \"end\": 221.84, \"text\": \"an affair with Barry while he was being paid to be her bodyguard.\"}, {\"start\": 221.84, \"end\": 226.88, \"text\": \"Authorities would not say if the nude pictures were of Barry.\"}, {\"start\": 229.88, \"end\": 235.08, \"text\": \"There may soon be some changes to gun laws in Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 235.08, \"end\": 250.06, \"text\": \"The state Senate approved the Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School Public Safety Act.\"}, {\"start\": 250.06, \"end\": 255.5, \"text\": \"The act says Floridians would have to be 21 years old before legally buying a gun.\"}, {\"start\": 255.5, \"end\": 263.3, \"text\": \"It would also establish a three day waiting period for most gun purchases and bans bump\"}, {\"start\": 263.3, \"end\": 265.86, \"text\": \"stocks.\"}, {\"start\": 265.86, \"end\": 273.66, \"text\": \"The measure passed the Senate by a narrow 20 to 18 margin and must now pass the House\"}, {\"start\": 273.66, \"end\": 279.98, \"text\": \"before going to Governor Rick Scott's desk.\"}, {\"start\": 283.16, \"end\": 293.9, \"text\": \"New Englanders hit by this weekend's deadly nor'easter will barely have time to clean\"}, {\"start\": 293.9, \"end\": 297.24, \"text\": \"up before another possible storm heads their way.\"}, {\"start\": 297.24, \"end\": 304.46, \"text\": \"The National Weather Service in Boston says the next nor'easter could come either Wednesday\"}, {\"start\": 304.46, \"end\": 311.96, \"text\": \"or Thursday of this week, bringing heavy snow, fierce winds and high waves to much of southern\"}, {\"start\": 311.96, \"end\": 313.86, \"text\": \"New England.\"}, {\"start\": 313.86, \"end\": 317.5, \"text\": \"That's not quite the news some were hoping for.\"}, {\"start\": 317.5, \"end\": 323.76, \"text\": \"Many of those residents are among the more than 500,000 customers from Virginia to\"}, {\"start\": 323.76, \"end\": 327.36, \"text\": \"Massachusetts who still don't have power.\"}, {\"start\": 330.72, \"end\": 337.469, \"text\": \"This is video from inside the West Virginia State Capitol.\"}, {\"start\": 337.469, \"end\": 346.12, \"text\": \"Thousands of teachers cheered after lawmakers reached a deal agreeing to give a 5% pay raise\"}, {\"start\": 346.12, \"end\": 350.5, \"text\": \"to all state employees, including teachers and school staff.\"}, {\"start\": 350.509, \"end\": 354.969, \"text\": \"Schools all over the state have been shut down for nine days because of the teachers'\"}, {\"start\": 354.969, \"end\": 357.089, \"text\": \"strike.\"}, {\"start\": 357.089, \"end\": 365.54, \"text\": \"Both the House and Senate unanimously approved the pay raise and the bill is expected to\"}, {\"start\": 365.54, \"end\": 371.92, \"text\": \"be signed by Governor Jim Justice today.\"}, {\"start\": 371.92, \"end\": 381.76, \"text\": \"A representative for the teachers' union anticipates school will be back in session on Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 385.36, \"end\": 398.2, \"text\": \"A new study from the journal \\\"Pediatrics\\\" suggests that encouraging teens to diet may\"}, {\"start\": 398.2, \"end\": 404.8, \"text\": \"affect their weight and emotional health as an adult.\"}, {\"start\": 404.8, \"end\": 409.7, \"text\": \"The study says this encouragement to diet can negatively impact the teen and it may\"}, {\"start\": 409.7, \"end\": 411.74, \"text\": \"affect their children too because they are likely to do the same with their kids.\"}, {\"start\": 411.74, \"end\": 422.94, \"text\": \"To help teens build a positive and healthy body image, start healthy habits when they\"}, {\"start\": 423.0, \"end\": 424.58, \"text\": \"are young.\"}, {\"start\": 424.58, \"end\": 426.58, \"text\": \"Be the example.\"}, {\"start\": 426.58, \"end\": 432.74, \"text\": \"If they see a parent eating healthy, they are more likely to develop that habit.\"}, {\"start\": 432.74, \"end\": 438.759, \"text\": \"Don't bribe children to eat vegetables or punish them if they refuse.\"}, {\"start\": 438.76, \"end\": 444.3, \"text\": \"Try teaching them that cooking and eating veggies is fun.\"}, {\"start\": 444.3, \"end\": 449.64, \"text\": \"Encourage a positive body image.\"}, {\"start\": 449.64, \"end\": 459.7, \"text\": \"Teach teens about the different body types and how one is no better than the other.\"}, {\"start\": 461.98, \"end\": 464.08, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 464.08, \"end\": 465.86, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 465.86, \"end\": 468.4, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 468.4, \"end\": 473.92, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 473.92, \"end\": 481.88, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "g2UTplDl6Qc": {
    "video_id": "g2UTplDl6Qc",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.17.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171118",
    "duration": 560,
    "view_count": 398,
    "description": "November 17, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-HEATED EXCHANGE IN TAX HEARING\n-ROY MOORE SUPPORTERS RALLY\n-TRUMP CONGRATULATES NCAA CHAMPIONS \n-26 MIGRANTS' BODIES LAID TO REST IN ITALY\n-PUERTO RICO'S HEAD OF POWER AUTHORITY RESIGNS\n-J-HUD PROTECTIVE ORDER AGAINST FIANCE\n-JESSE JACKSON DIAGNOSED WITH PARKINSON'S\n-NEARLY 51M EXPECTED TO TRAVEL FOR THANKSGIVING\n-DOG OWNERS HAVE LOWER RISK OF MORTALITY\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 10.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"I am Candace Jones and here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.025, \"end\": 17.025, \"text\": \"The White House is applauding the Senate\"}, {\"start\": 17.1, \"end\": 21.0, \"text\": \"Finance Committee after they approved the GOP tax\"}, {\"start\": 21.0, \"end\": 26.0, \"text\": \"plan. But it wasn't all\"}, {\"start\": 26.0, \"end\": 31.0, \"text\": \"smooth sailing. During the meeting, Democratic\"}, {\"start\": 31.0, \"end\": 36.0, \"text\": \"Senator Sherrod Brown accused\"}, {\"start\": 36.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"Republicans of cutting taxes for\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 49.0, \"text\": \"the rich. That set off Republican Senator Orrin Hatch.\"}, {\"start\": 49.0, \"end\": 54.0, \"text\": \"Hatch firmly reminded Brown that he came\"}, {\"start\": 54.0, \"end\": 59.0, \"text\": \"from poor people and has been working his entire political\"}, {\"start\": 59.0, \"end\": 64.0, \"text\": \"career to help people who don't have a chance.\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 69.0, \"text\": \"And he said he resents anybody who says he's just\"}, {\"start\": 69.0, \"end\": 74.0, \"text\": \"doing this for the rich. The heated exchange\"}, {\"start\": 74.0, \"end\": 79.0, \"text\": \"came as the Senate Finance Committee was wrapping\"}, {\"start\": 79.0, \"end\": 84.0, \"text\": \"up debate on the new GOP tax plan.\"}, {\"start\": 84.0, \"end\": 90.0, \"text\": \"The committee approved the plan and now it goes to the Senate for a full vote.\"}, {\"start\": 92.0, \"end\": 96.0, \"text\": \"The wife of Alabama Republican Roy Moore\"}, {\"start\": 96.0, \"end\": 101.0, \"text\": \"spoke on the steps of the state\"}, {\"start\": 102.0, \"end\": 106.0, \"text\": \"Capitol building today.\"}, {\"start\": 107.0, \"end\": 112.0, \"text\": \"Kayla Moore boldly announced her husband will\"}, {\"start\": 112.0, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"not end his quest for the U.S. Senate.\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 124.0, \"text\": \"She was surrounded by many women who praised her\"}, {\"start\": 124.0, \"end\": 129.0, \"text\": \"husband's virtues and insisted he\"}, {\"start\": 129.0, \"end\": 134.0, \"text\": \"isn't going anywhere. Several women have accused Moore\"}, {\"start\": 134.0, \"end\": 139.0, \"text\": \"of behaving inappropriately with them when they were teenagers\"}, {\"start\": 140.0, \"end\": 145.0, \"text\": \"and he was in his 30s.\"}, {\"start\": 145.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"Moore will face Democrat Doug Jones in a special\"}, {\"start\": 149.0, \"end\": 154.0, \"text\": \"election on December 12th.\"}, {\"start\": 156.0, \"end\": 160.0, \"text\": \"It was a busy but celebratory day\"}, {\"start\": 160.0, \"end\": 166.0, \"text\": \"for President Trump. The White House hosted\"}, {\"start\": 166.0, \"end\": 173.0, \"text\": \"18 NCAA championship teams today.\"}, {\"start\": 173.0, \"end\": 177.0, \"text\": \"The teams posed for pictures with the president,\"}, {\"start\": 177.0, \"end\": 181.0, \"text\": \"they were granted a tour of the Oval Office and were\"}, {\"start\": 181.0, \"end\": 187.0, \"text\": \"honored with a formal reception.\"}, {\"start\": 187.0, \"end\": 191.0, \"text\": \"The University of South Carolina's championship\"}, {\"start\": 191.0, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"women's basketball team\"}, {\"start\": 196.0, \"end\": 199.0, \"text\": \"was not in attendance. The team declined the invitation.\"}, {\"start\": 200.0, \"end\": 206.0, \"text\": \"It was a somber day in Salerno, Italy.\"}, {\"start\": 206.0, \"end\": 210.0, \"text\": \"The town held a funeral for 26 migrants who\"}, {\"start\": 210.0, \"end\": 218.0, \"text\": \"drowned in the Mediterranean earlier this month.\"}, {\"start\": 218.0, \"end\": 222.0, \"text\": \"They were all women from Africa,\"}, {\"start\": 222.0, \"end\": 226.0, \"text\": \"most of them just in their teens.\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 231.0, \"text\": \"It's believed they boarded a flimsy rubber boat in Libya\"}, {\"start\": 231.0, \"end\": 236.0, \"text\": \"in hopes of getting to Europe\"}, {\"start\": 237.0, \"end\": 243.0, \"text\": \"for a better life. But it ended in tragedy.\"}, {\"start\": 243.0, \"end\": 248.0, \"text\": \"Now investigators are determined to try to shine a light on\"}, {\"start\": 248.0, \"end\": 253.0, \"text\": \"why these women were coming to Italy. They believe the girls were\"}, {\"start\": 253.0, \"end\": 258.0, \"text\": \"victims of sex trafficking,\"}, {\"start\": 258.0, \"end\": 262.0, \"text\": \"which is a growing industry in Italy\"}, {\"start\": 263.0, \"end\": 268.0, \"text\": \"and through out Europe.\"}, {\"start\": 270.001, \"end\": 272.099, \"text\": \"Ricardo Ramos,\"}, {\"start\": 272.1, \"end\": 277.0, \"text\": \"the head of Puerto Rico's Power Authority,\"}, {\"start\": 277.0, \"end\": 281.0, \"text\": \"has stepped down. His resignation comes\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 285.0, \"text\": \"nearly two months after Hurricane Maria\"}, {\"start\": 285.0, \"end\": 290.0, \"text\": \"left most of the island without electricity.\"}, {\"start\": 290.0, \"end\": 295.0, \"text\": \"Ramos took over as head of the Power\"}, {\"start\": 295.0, \"end\": 299.0, \"text\": \"Authority last year. Puerto Rico officials did not say\"}, {\"start\": 300.0, \"end\": 304.0, \"text\": \"why Ramos was resigning but the agency\"}, {\"start\": 305.0, \"end\": 310.0, \"text\": \"has faced severe criticism for signing a 300 million dollar\"}, {\"start\": 310.0, \"end\": 314.0, \"text\": \"contract with a small Montana firm\"}, {\"start\": 314.0, \"end\": 317.0, \"text\": \"that only had two employees at the time\"}, {\"start\": 317.024, \"end\": 324.924, \"text\": \"the contract was signed.\"}, {\"start\": 326.025, \"end\": 328.999, \"text\": \"Singer Jennifer\"}, {\"start\": 329.0, \"end\": 333.0, \"text\": \"Hudson has received a protective order\"}, {\"start\": 333.0, \"end\": 338.0, \"text\": \"against her former fiance David Otunda.\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 343.0, \"text\": \"The pair had been together for 10 years and have an 8 year old son. According to\"}, {\"start\": 343.0, \"end\": 348.0, \"text\": \"Hudson's representation the couple have been\"}, {\"start\": 348.0, \"end\": 353.0, \"text\": \"ending their relationship for months.\"}, {\"start\": 353.0, \"end\": 357.0, \"text\": \"The reason for the protective order\"}, {\"start\": 357.0, \"end\": 361.0, \"text\": \"is still unknown but Hudson says\"}, {\"start\": 361.024, \"end\": 363.024, \"text\": \"it is in the best interest of her son.\"}, {\"start\": 365.025, \"end\": 366.925, \"text\": \"Civil rights activist\"}, {\"start\": 367.0, \"end\": 371.0, \"text\": \"Reverend Jesse Jackson\"}, {\"start\": 371.0, \"end\": 376.0, \"text\": \"announced that he has been diagnosed with\"}, {\"start\": 376.0, \"end\": 382.0, \"text\": \"Parkinson's. Parkinson's disease is a neurological\"}, {\"start\": 382.0, \"end\": 387.0, \"text\": \"disorder that causes tremors,\"}, {\"start\": 387.0, \"end\": 393.0, \"text\": \"stiffness, difficulty balancing, walking and\"}, {\"start\": 393.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"coordinating movements. There is no cure.\"}, {\"start\": 398.0, \"end\": 403.0, \"text\": \"Jackson says he started to notice changes in his body\"}, {\"start\": 404.0, \"end\": 409.0, \"text\": \"about three years ago. He says his father\"}, {\"start\": 409.0, \"end\": 413.0, \"text\": \"also died from complications caused by\"}, {\"start\": 413.0, \"end\": 418.0, \"text\": \"Parkinson's. Jackson says he will now start to make lifestyle\"}, {\"start\": 418.0, \"end\": 423.0, \"text\": \"changes and dedicate himself to physical therapy\"}, {\"start\": 423.0, \"end\": 429.0, \"text\": \"in hopes of slowing the disease.\"}, {\"start\": 430.001, \"end\": 434.099, \"text\": \"According to Triple-A nearly 51 million Americans\"}, {\"start\": 434.1, \"end\": 438.0, \"text\": \"are expected to travel at least 50 miles\"}, {\"start\": 438.0, \"end\": 443.0, \"text\": \"away from home over the upcoming Thanksgiving holiday week.\"}, {\"start\": 443.0, \"end\": 448.0, \"text\": \"That's an increase of 3.3 percent over last year. Triple-A projects an additional\"}, {\"start\": 448.0, \"end\": 452.0, \"text\": \"1.6 million people will travel by airplane,\"}, {\"start\": 452.0, \"end\": 457.0, \"text\": \"car or train this year compared to last year.\"}, {\"start\": 457.0, \"end\": 462.0, \"text\": \"That's the highest travel volume since 2005.\"}, {\"start\": 462.0, \"end\": 467.0, \"text\": \"The holiday week officially starts Wednesday November 22nd\"}, {\"start\": 467.0, \"end\": 470.0, \"text\": \"and ends Sunday November 26th.\"}, {\"start\": 471.0, \"end\": 476.0, \"text\": \"If you are a dog owner your dog could\"}, {\"start\": 477.0, \"end\": 482.0, \"text\": \"literally be saving your life. According to a new study\"}, {\"start\": 483.0, \"end\": 487.0, \"text\": \"dog ownership is associated with a lower risk\"}, {\"start\": 487.0, \"end\": 492.0, \"text\": \"of cardiovascular disease and death. The biggest beneficiaries\"}, {\"start\": 492.0, \"end\": 497.0, \"text\": \"are single people. Their overall risk of death\"}, {\"start\": 497.0, \"end\": 502.0, \"text\": \"dropped to 33 percent and their risk of cardiovascular related deaths\"}, {\"start\": 502.0, \"end\": 509.0, \"text\": \"fell by 36 percent compared to single\"}, {\"start\": 509.0, \"end\": 513.0, \"text\": \"individuals who do not own a dog. The study also found\"}, {\"start\": 514.0, \"end\": 517.0, \"text\": \"that owners of\"}, {\"start\": 518.0, \"end\": 523.0, \"text\": \"hunting breeds like terriers,\"}, {\"start\": 523.0, \"end\": 527.0, \"text\": \"retrievers and scent hounds\"}, {\"start\": 527.024, \"end\": 532.024, \"text\": \"got the most protection.\"}, {\"start\": 534.025, \"end\": 537.025, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 537.1, \"end\": 540.1, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 540.1, \"end\": 544.1, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 545.024, \"end\": 550.024, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "oUUWMIk-GUw": {
    "video_id": "oUUWMIk-GUw",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.5.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180406",
    "duration": 420,
    "view_count": 929,
    "description": "4.5.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Trump orders U.S. National Guard to Mexico border\n-Missing CDC employee found dead\n-2018 Ford Escape fails passenger crash test\n-Teacher's broken chair sparks $44,000 in donations\n-Lose your wealth, Lose your health\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.98, \"end\": 9.16, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.16, \"end\": 11.64, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.68, \"end\": 13.28, \"text\": \"I’m Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 13.28, \"end\": 16.36, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.7, \"end\": 30.46, \"text\": \"President Trump officially signed a memorandum to deploy the National Guard to the southern border.\"}, {\"start\": 30.46, \"end\": 35.7, \"text\": \"The memorandum announced that the security of the United States is imperiled by a drastic\"}, {\"start\": 35.7, \"end\": 39.82, \"text\": \"surge of illegal activity on the southern border.\"}, {\"start\": 40.0, \"end\": 46.72, \"text\": \"Data from a Department of Homeland Security study last fall shows illegal border crossings\"}, {\"start\": 46.8, \"end\": 56.72, \"text\": \"through 2016 for at their lowest point in nearly 5 decades.\"}, {\"start\": 56.72, \"end\": 65.36, \"text\": \"Recently new border patrol statistics show a 37% increase in attempted border crossings\"}, {\"start\": 65.36, \"end\": 67.52, \"text\": \"in the last month.\"}, {\"start\": 67.52, \"end\": 75.92, \"text\": \"The secretary of Homeland Security says the military is looking into options to build\"}, {\"start\": 75.93, \"end\": 80.86, \"text\": \"a wall on military installations on the border.\"}, {\"start\": 80.86, \"end\": 87.74, \"text\": \"The Wall Street Journal reports that US officials are planning to build a wall along part of\"}, {\"start\": 87.76, \"end\": 94.16, \"text\": \"a bombing range along the Arizona/Mexico border.\"}, {\"start\": 94.16, \"end\": 103.28, \"text\": \"But the military installation only covers 31 of the nearly 2,000 mile-long border.\"}, {\"start\": 104.88, \"end\": 115.439, \"text\": \"Officials in Georgia say there were no signs of foul play in the death of 35-year-old CDC\"}, {\"start\": 115.44, \"end\": 119.0, \"text\": \"scientist Timothy Cunningham, who went missing in February.\"}, {\"start\": 119.0, \"end\": 128.4, \"text\": \"Cunningham’s remains were found in a river Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 128.4, \"end\": 135.6, \"text\": \"According to the medical examiner, the cause of death has been listed as drowning, but\"}, {\"start\": 135.6, \"end\": 139.4, \"text\": \"the manner of death has not been determined.\"}, {\"start\": 139.4, \"end\": 147.84, \"text\": \"Cunningham was last seen on February 12 shortly after police say a supervisor told him why\"}, {\"start\": 147.84, \"end\": 149.96, \"text\": \"he was being passed over for a promotion.\"}, {\"start\": 149.96, \"end\": 154.44, \"text\": \"The director of the CDC issued a statement last month denying Cunningham have been denied\"}, {\"start\": 154.44, \"end\": 160.0, \"text\": \"a promotion, saying he had been promoted in July.\"}, {\"start\": 160.0, \"end\": 163.8, \"text\": \"The case perplexed investigators because Cunningham’s\"}, {\"start\": 163.8, \"end\": 167.24, \"text\": \"keys, cell phone, credit cards, debit cards,\"}, {\"start\": 167.24, \"end\": 175.16, \"text\": \"wallet and all forms of identification were found in his house, along with his beloved dog.\"}, {\"start\": 176.44, \"end\": 187.43, \"text\": \"The Ford Escape has failed a new passenger side crash test designed to show how well\"}, {\"start\": 187.44, \"end\": 199.04, \"text\": \"front seat passengers are protected in a violent collision.\"}, {\"start\": 199.04, \"end\": 207.68, \"text\": \"The test mimics the impact of a vehicle with another car or a tree or pole.\"}, {\"start\": 207.68, \"end\": 218.35, \"text\": \"The 2018 Ford Escape earned a poor rating because the cabin was crushed inward and the\"}, {\"start\": 218.35, \"end\": 221.08, \"text\": \"side airbags did not deploy.\"}, {\"start\": 221.08, \"end\": 229.32, \"text\": \"The Escape was the only small SUV in a group of seven tested to not pass.\"}, {\"start\": 229.32, \"end\": 235.12, \"text\": \"Ford says the Escape has earned high marks in all other government and insurance institute\"}, {\"start\": 235.12, \"end\": 240.36, \"text\": \"crash tests.\"}, {\"start\": 240.36, \"end\": 245.75, \"text\": \"In a statement Ford said “safety continues to be one of the highest priorities in the\"}, {\"start\": 245.76, \"end\": 248.36, \"text\": \"design of our vehicles.”\"}, {\"start\": 249.48, \"end\": 261.96, \"text\": \"Oklahoma teacher Laurissa Kovac posted pictures of broken chairs on Facebook to\"}, {\"start\": 262.12, \"end\": 263.84, \"text\": \"raise awareness about the conditions in her\"}, {\"start\": 263.84, \"end\": 265.36, \"text\": \"classroom.\"}, {\"start\": 265.36, \"end\": 269.52, \"text\": \"Kovac is one of hundreds of Oklahoma teachers participating in a walkout to demand\"}, {\"start\": 269.53, \"end\": 275.62, \"text\": \"increased funding for schools and higher wages for educators.\"}, {\"start\": 275.62, \"end\": 283.84, \"text\": \"Kovac's photo of a broken chair was shared more than 82,000 times.\"}, {\"start\": 283.88, \"end\": 288.08, \"text\": \"People asked how they could help.\"}, {\"start\": 288.08, \"end\": 295.44, \"text\": \"She set up an Amazon registry on March 30.\"}, {\"start\": 295.44, \"end\": 304.76, \"text\": \"So far she’s received more than 600 packages and more than $44,000 in supplies.\"}, {\"start\": 304.76, \"end\": 308.52, \"text\": \"Kovac says she will be sharing it all with other teachers.\"}, {\"start\": 309.8, \"end\": 316.64, \"text\": \"There may be a link between your finances and your health.\"}, {\"start\": 316.64, \"end\": 323.8, \"text\": \"A new study suggests losing your life savings can also cost you your life.\"}, {\"start\": 323.8, \"end\": 330.24, \"text\": \"Researchers are offering scientific proof that this might actually be true.\"}, {\"start\": 330.24, \"end\": 339.64, \"text\": \"A new study found that adults between the ages of 51 and 61, who lost 75% or more of\"}, {\"start\": 339.64, \"end\": 348.04, \"text\": \"their wealth over two years, faced an increased risk of dying over the next two decades.\"}, {\"start\": 348.04, \"end\": 353.84, \"text\": \"Scientists studied people experiencing a sudden “negative wealth shock.”\"}, {\"start\": 353.84, \"end\": 361.36, \"text\": \"That means they lost most of their assets including their homes or businesses over two years.\"}, {\"start\": 361.36, \"end\": 368.8, \"text\": \"The study also found that people who experienced that massive hit on their nest egg were more\"}, {\"start\": 368.8, \"end\": 374.72, \"text\": \"likely to be women or non-Hispanic white and have lower household income.\"}, {\"start\": 374.72, \"end\": 386.88, \"text\": \"Researchers believe a large money crisis causes major stress that impacts the body over time.\"}, {\"start\": 386.88, \"end\": 393.84, \"text\": \"Previous studies have shown a link between financial instability and increased risk of\"}, {\"start\": 393.92, \"end\": 397.92, \"text\": \"depression and substance abuse.\"}, {\"start\": 399.76, \"end\": 402.56, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 402.56, \"end\": 404.28, \"text\": \"I’m Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 404.28, \"end\": 407.68, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 407.68, \"end\": 412.28, \"text\": \"Remember to like this on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}]"
  },
  "MrQeObIhUXU": {
    "video_id": "MrQeObIhUXU",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.20.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180421",
    "duration": 382,
    "view_count": 1382,
    "description": "4.20.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-A school shooting in Florida\n-National School Walkout on Columbine anniversary\n-DNC is suing Trump campaign, Russia and WikiLeaks\n-Two Florida Deputies killed in Ambush\n-Woman wanted for murder is captured\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN, FOX, AB",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.48, \"end\": 8.76, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.76, \"end\": 11.18, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.18, \"end\": 12.68, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.68, \"end\": 16.48, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.66, \"end\": 27.86, \"text\": \"There was a high school shooting in Ocala, Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 27.86, \"end\": 33.84, \"text\": \"One student is injured and another is in custody.\"}, {\"start\": 33.84, \"end\": 41.82, \"text\": \"According to the spokesman, the victim at Forest High School was shot in the ankle.\"}, {\"start\": 41.82, \"end\": 48.48, \"text\": \"The victim was hospitalized but his condition is not life-threatening.\"}, {\"start\": 48.48, \"end\": 58.0, \"text\": \"Emergency vehicles surrounded the school after the shooting and authorities asked residents\"}, {\"start\": 58.0, \"end\": 61.14, \"text\": \"to avoid the area.\"}, {\"start\": 61.14, \"end\": 69.64, \"text\": \"Students were being bused to a nearby church for parents to pick them up.\"}, {\"start\": 69.64, \"end\": 80.74, \"text\": \"It comes more than two months after the mass shooting at Marjorie Stoneman Douglas High\"}, {\"start\": 80.74, \"end\": 86.54, \"text\": \"School in Parkland, Florida which left 17 people dead.\"}, {\"start\": 86.54, \"end\": 91.58, \"text\": \"It also marks the 20th school shooting this year.\"}, {\"start\": 91.58, \"end\": 98.28, \"text\": \"Forest High was one of roughly 2,500 schools nationwide said to participate in Friday's\"}, {\"start\": 98.28, \"end\": 103.96, \"text\": \"national school walkout against gun violence.\"}, {\"start\": 105.66, \"end\": 115.22, \"text\": \"April 20 is the 19th anniversary of the Columbine school shooting where 12 students and one\"}, {\"start\": 115.22, \"end\": 118.54, \"text\": \"teacher were killed.\"}, {\"start\": 118.54, \"end\": 129.44, \"text\": \"Walkout organizers say elected officials haven't done enough since Columbine.\"}, {\"start\": 129.44, \"end\": 132.68, \"text\": \"In remembrance of the Columbine shooting more\"}, {\"start\": 132.68, \"end\": 138.36, \"text\": \"than 2,500 walkouts are expected at schools across the country.\"}, {\"start\": 138.36, \"end\": 148.52, \"text\": \"The idea for the walkout came from national school walkout founder Lane Murdock.\"}, {\"start\": 148.52, \"end\": 152.52, \"text\": \"Murdock is a 16-year-old sophomore from Connecticut.\"}, {\"start\": 152.52, \"end\": 155.6, \"text\": \"She has a three-part goal.\"}, {\"start\": 155.6, \"end\": 160.76, \"text\": \"First hold elected officials accountable.\"}, {\"start\": 160.76, \"end\": 167.0, \"text\": \"Number 2: promote solutions to gun violence.\"}, {\"start\": 167.0, \"end\": 172.7, \"text\": \"Number 3:  remove the mystery and engage students in the political system.\"}, {\"start\": 172.7, \"end\": 181.48, \"text\": \"The walkout will also include a moment of silence for the victims of the Columbine tragedy.\"}, {\"start\": 182.5, \"end\": 194.22, \"text\": \"The Democratic National Committee filed a lawsuit against Russia, the Trump campaign\"}, {\"start\": 194.22, \"end\": 202.34, \"text\": \"and WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange.\"}, {\"start\": 202.34, \"end\": 210.08, \"text\": \"The lawsuit claims WikiLeaks published thousands of hacked DNC emails days before the 2016\"}, {\"start\": 210.08, \"end\": 212.48, \"text\": \"Democratic national convention.\"}, {\"start\": 212.48, \"end\": 224.92, \"text\": \"The emails included messages disparaging Hillary Clinton's 2016 primary opponent Bernie Sanders.\"}, {\"start\": 224.92, \"end\": 231.44, \"text\": \"The lawsuit also alleges Russia work with Trump advisers before the election to share\"}, {\"start\": 231.44, \"end\": 234.92, \"text\": \"material from the DNC cyber attack.\"}, {\"start\": 234.92, \"end\": 248.8, \"text\": \"The suit also names former Trump campaign chairman Paul Manafort and Trump advisers\"}, {\"start\": 248.8, \"end\": 253.0, \"text\": \"and others who attended a meeting with Russian officials.\"}, {\"start\": 253.0, \"end\": 259.6, \"text\": \"President Trump says his campaign did not help in Russia's election meddling.\"}, {\"start\": 261.6, \"end\": 271.4, \"text\": \"Two deputies were shot and killed while having lunch in a restaurant in Trenton, Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 271.4, \"end\": 277.68, \"text\": \"The shooter John Hubert shot officers through a window from outside the restaurant.\"}, {\"start\": 277.68, \"end\": 283.28, \"text\": \"When police arrived on the scene Hubert was found dead outside the restaurant.\"}, {\"start\": 283.28, \"end\": 286.04, \"text\": \"The shooting is under investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 286.04, \"end\": 290.12, \"text\": \"There is no motive at this time.\"}, {\"start\": 292.64, \"end\": 303.72, \"text\": \"U.S. Marshals in Texas have arrested a grandmother accused of murder in Minnesota and Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 303.72, \"end\": 308.92, \"text\": \"56-year-old Lois Riess was found in a South Padre Island restaurant.\"}, {\"start\": 308.92, \"end\": 317.16, \"text\": \"A witness spotted her and called the police.\"}, {\"start\": 317.16, \"end\": 321.8, \"text\": \"There has been national manhunt for Riess after she allegedly murdered her\"}, {\"start\": 321.8, \"end\": 326.68, \"text\": \"husband in Minnesota two months ago.\"}, {\"start\": 326.68, \"end\": 335.52, \"text\": \"She fled to Florida where she is also wanted for killing Pamela Hutchinson.\"}, {\"start\": 335.52, \"end\": 341.68, \"text\": \"Authorities say her motive for that murder was stealing Hutchinson's identity.\"}, {\"start\": 341.68, \"end\": 350.12, \"text\": \"Florida police want her extradited there so they can charge her in Hutchinson's murder.\"}, {\"start\": 352.96, \"end\": 355.12, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories today.\"}, {\"start\": 355.12, \"end\": 356.74, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 356.74, \"end\": 359.699, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 359.699, \"end\": 365.69, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 365.69, \"end\": 367.72, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 367.76, \"end\": 369.7, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 369.7, \"end\": 373.24, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "GMAOpKhvlPo": {
    "video_id": "GMAOpKhvlPo",
    "title": "Police ask for calm in Stephon Clark protests (ASL - 3.27.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180328",
    "duration": 74,
    "view_count": 157,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.46, \"end\": 11.5, \"text\": \"The police chief in Sacramento is asking protesters to exercise calm to prevent any more tragedies,\"}, {\"start\": 11.5, \"end\": 15.52, \"text\": \"injuries or property damage.\"}, {\"start\": 15.52, \"end\": 22.779, \"text\": \"The marchers are protesting the shooting death of Stephon Clark.\"}, {\"start\": 22.78, \"end\": 29.96, \"text\": \"Last week police fired 20 rounds at him while he was standing in his grandmother's backyard.\"}, {\"start\": 29.96, \"end\": 33.3, \"text\": \"He was struck multiple times and was pronounced dead at the scene.\"}, {\"start\": 33.3, \"end\": 37.44, \"text\": \"Police say they thought Clark was pointing a gun at them when in actuality he was only\"}, {\"start\": 37.56, \"end\": 39.96, \"text\": \"holding a cell phone.\"}, {\"start\": 39.96, \"end\": 46.88, \"text\": \"Because emotions are running extremely high in this case, Sacramento officials have asked\"}, {\"start\": 46.88, \"end\": 51.08, \"text\": \"the state's Attorney General to step in and conduct an independent investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 51.08, \"end\": 56.32, \"text\": \"Both police officers involved in the shooting have been placed on paid administrative leave.\"}, {\"start\": 56.32, \"end\": 60.72, \"text\": \"Their names have not been released.\"}, {\"start\": 60.84, \"end\": 70.6, \"text\": \"A GoFundMe account set up to help Clark's family with funeral expenses has already raised\"}, {\"start\": 70.72, \"end\": 73.24, \"text\": \"nearly $62,000.\"}]"
  },
  "VN9X1WQKjWI": {
    "video_id": "VN9X1WQKjWI",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.20.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180321",
    "duration": 496,
    "view_count": 1290,
    "description": "3.20.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Maryland school shooter dead, 2 injured\n-Package explodes at Fedex facility in Texas \n-Nikolas Cruz's brother in court\n-\"Sex in the City\" star holds 1st Governor campaign event\n-Facebook stock drops, Zuckerberg silent\n-United Airlines suspends pet shipping\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.2, \"end\": 7.48, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.48, \"end\": 9.86, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.86, \"end\": 11.18, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 11.18, \"end\": 14.04, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.26, \"end\": 29.94, \"text\": \"Just before 8 AM Tuesday morning, police say 17-year-old Austin Rollins shot a male and\"}, {\"start\": 29.94, \"end\": 33.87, \"text\": \"female student in the hallway at Great Mills high school in Maryland.\"}, {\"start\": 33.87, \"end\": 39.679, \"text\": \"Witnesses say the school's resource officer responded to the scene in less than one minute\"}, {\"start\": 39.68, \"end\": 41.62, \"text\": \"and he and Rollins simultaneously exchanged gunfire.\"}, {\"start\": 41.62, \"end\": 46.3, \"text\": \"Rollins was killed, the officer was unharmed.\"}, {\"start\": 46.34, \"end\": 53.94, \"text\": \"The 16-year-old female student Rollins shot is listed in critical condition and the 14-year-old\"}, {\"start\": 53.94, \"end\": 59.0, \"text\": \"male student is listed in stable condition.\"}, {\"start\": 59.06, \"end\": 64.72, \"text\": \"Authorities say Rollins was in a prior relationship with the female student but they are not sure\"}, {\"start\": 64.72, \"end\": 67.2, \"text\": \"if that factored into Rollins' motive for the shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 67.2, \"end\": 74.12, \"text\": \"Investigators are now collecting forensic evidence from multiple crime scenes and looking\"}, {\"start\": 74.12, \"end\": 80.74, \"text\": \"through electronic devices owned by Rollins.\"}, {\"start\": 80.74, \"end\": 88.98, \"text\": \"This is the 17th school shooting in the United States since January 1.\"}, {\"start\": 91.84, \"end\": 97.4, \"text\": \"There have been four package explosions in Austin, Texas this month.\"}, {\"start\": 97.4, \"end\": 106.38, \"text\": \"Today a fifth package exploded, this time at a FedEx sorting facility near San Antonio.\"}, {\"start\": 106.38, \"end\": 108.52, \"text\": \"One FedEx worker was injured.\"}, {\"start\": 108.56, \"end\": 111.32, \"text\": \"Investigators say the package was traveling along the automated conveyor belt when it exploded.\"}, {\"start\": 111.32, \"end\": 117.24, \"text\": \"Investigators say they found a second package with explosives packed inside and both packages\"}, {\"start\": 117.24, \"end\": 122.4, \"text\": \"were sent using a private delivery service.\"}, {\"start\": 122.56, \"end\": 127.36, \"text\": \"Authorities are trying to figure out if all the blasts are connected and if it is\"}, {\"start\": 127.36, \"end\": 131.64, \"text\": \"the work of a serial bomber.\"}, {\"start\": 131.64, \"end\": 139.92, \"text\": \"Until they get answers, police are warning everyone in the area to stay on high alert.\"}, {\"start\": 142.36, \"end\": 153.52, \"text\": \"Zachary Cruz, the younger brother of accused Parkland, Florida school shooter Nikolas\"}, {\"start\": 153.52, \"end\": 157.26, \"text\": \"Cruz, was in court Tuesday afternoon.\"}, {\"start\": 157.26, \"end\": 168.48, \"text\": \"He was arrested Monday and charged with trespassing.\"}, {\"start\": 168.48, \"end\": 178.2, \"text\": \"Police say the 18-year-old rode his skateboard through the campus of Marjory Stoneman Douglas\"}, {\"start\": 178.2, \"end\": 185.32, \"text\": \"high school after getting through the locked doors and gates.\"}, {\"start\": 185.32, \"end\": 192.16, \"text\": \"According to his arrest report, Cruz said he wanted to reflect on the school shooting\"}, {\"start\": 192.16, \"end\": 195.56, \"text\": \"that killed 17 people last month.\"}, {\"start\": 195.56, \"end\": 205.799, \"text\": \"A judge set Cruz's bond at $500,000, ordered him to wear an ankle monitor, have no contact\"}, {\"start\": 205.8, \"end\": 216.08, \"text\": \"with his brother and stay out of Broward County except for court dates.\"}, {\"start\": 216.08, \"end\": 223.56, \"text\": \"Cruz's defense attorney protested the judge's ruling saying his client was being punished\"}, {\"start\": 223.56, \"end\": 226.32, \"text\": \"for his brother Nikolas' crimes.\"}, {\"start\": 228.32, \"end\": 243.52, \"text\": \"Former \\\"Sex In The City\\\" actress Cynthia Nixon is running for governor of New York.\"}, {\"start\": 243.52, \"end\": 251.04, \"text\": \"She announced her candidacy on Twitter on Monday and hit the campaign trail on Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 251.04, \"end\": 260.72, \"text\": \"She spoke at the Bethesda Healing Center, a church with a predominately African-American\"}, {\"start\": 260.72, \"end\": 263.36, \"text\": \"congregation.\"}, {\"start\": 263.36, \"end\": 272.96, \"text\": \"The 51-year-old will challenge incumbent Governor Andrew Cuomo in the Democratic primary in\"}, {\"start\": 272.96, \"end\": 277.4, \"text\": \"September.\"}, {\"start\": 277.4, \"end\": 284.34, \"text\": \"Nixon says New York leaders are letting the people down.\"}, {\"start\": 284.34, \"end\": 292.449, \"text\": \"Besides being an actress, Nixon is also known as an activist for education and equality.\"}, {\"start\": 292.449, \"end\": 296.889, \"text\": \"And she was recently honored by the Human Rights campaign for her work advocating for\"}, {\"start\": 296.889, \"end\": 308.86, \"text\": \"marriage equality and fighting stigma and prejudice.\"}, {\"start\": 308.86, \"end\": 314.879, \"text\": \"Facebook is facing mounting questions about how its user data came to be harvested for\"}, {\"start\": 314.88, \"end\": 322.76, \"text\": \"political purposes -- and its stock is suffering as a result.\"}, {\"start\": 322.76, \"end\": 330.82, \"text\": \"Facebook shares fell by 3% on Tuesday after suffering its biggest one-day fall in four years.\"}, {\"start\": 330.82, \"end\": 339.38, \"text\": \"Since Friday, the company has lost $49 billion in market value.\"}, {\"start\": 339.38, \"end\": 351.92, \"text\": \"Facebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg's net worth plummeted too, down about $5 million.\"}, {\"start\": 351.92, \"end\": 363.86, \"text\": \"The loss coincides with news that data from Cambridge Analytica, which had ties to Donald\"}, {\"start\": 363.86, \"end\": 371.88, \"text\": \"Trump's presidential campaign, reportedly accessed information from about 50 million\"}, {\"start\": 371.88, \"end\": 376.2, \"text\": \"Facebook users.\"}, {\"start\": 376.2, \"end\": 382.94, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg has not commented publicly since the story broke late on Friday and sources\"}, {\"start\": 382.94, \"end\": 391.54, \"text\": \"say that is frustrating many executives inside the company.\"}, {\"start\": 393.04, \"end\": 399.0, \"text\": \"United Airlines says effective immediately it will stop accepting new reservations for\"}, {\"start\": 399.0, \"end\": 402.46, \"text\": \"its \\\"Petsafe\\\"program.\"}, {\"start\": 402.46, \"end\": 409.48, \"text\": \"The program is for animals that are traveling alone in the cargo area.\"}, {\"start\": 409.48, \"end\": 415.54, \"text\": \"The suspension does not affect pets accompanied by passengers in the cabin.\"}, {\"start\": 415.54, \"end\": 422.04, \"text\": \"If you have, however, already made reservations through the program, the airline will honor it.\"}, {\"start\": 422.04, \"end\": 429.48, \"text\": \"The policy change comes in the wake of recent mishaps involving the airline and pets.\"}, {\"start\": 429.48, \"end\": 436.86, \"text\": \"Last week a French bulldog died after a flight attendant told its owner that it needed to\"}, {\"start\": 436.86, \"end\": 442.04, \"text\": \"be put in the overhead luggage bin.\"}, {\"start\": 442.04, \"end\": 450.879, \"text\": \"A few days later a dog that was supposed to go to Kansas was mistakenly shipped to Japan.\"}, {\"start\": 450.88, \"end\": 458.84, \"text\": \"United officials say they are conducting a thorough and systematic review of their program.\"}, {\"start\": 458.84, \"end\": 463.04, \"text\": \"The review is expected to be completed by May 1.\"}, {\"start\": 466.0, \"end\": 468.52, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 468.52, \"end\": 469.82, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 469.82, \"end\": 473.98, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 473.98, \"end\": 479.38, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 479.38, \"end\": 487.2, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "MiENdjCKv1s": {
    "video_id": "MiENdjCKv1s",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.31.18: News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180201",
    "duration": 540,
    "view_count": 947,
    "description": "1.31.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Fallout from Larry Nassar case continues\n-Train with congress members hits truck, one person killed\n-State of the Union sets up immigration showdown\n-Head of CDC resigns\n-Super blue blood moon across the globe\n-Super Bowl ad: Lexus/Black Panther sneak peak\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in Americ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.84, \"end\": 7.62, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.62, \"end\": 10.42, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.42, \"end\": 11.66, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 11.66, \"end\": 14.2, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.48, \"end\": 23.92, \"text\": \"A new interim president was named at Michigan State University Wednesday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 23.92, \"end\": 29.32, \"text\": \"And the entire board of USA gymnastics has resigned.\"}, {\"start\": 29.42, \"end\": 38.86, \"text\": \"All because former sports physician Larry Nassar was allowed to abuse young girls unchecked\"}, {\"start\": 38.86, \"end\": 40.66, \"text\": \"for over 20 years.\"}, {\"start\": 40.66, \"end\": 47.96, \"text\": \"This week Nassar is hearing from more of his victims as he enters the sentencing phase\"}, {\"start\": 48.04, \"end\": 50.32, \"text\": \"in a second Michigan county.\"}, {\"start\": 50.32, \"end\": 56.26, \"text\": \"At least 65 women are expected to speak in an Eaton County, Michigan courtroom about\"}, {\"start\": 56.26, \"end\": 58.48, \"text\": \"being sexually assaulted by Nassar.\"}, {\"start\": 58.48, \"end\": 68.88, \"text\": \"He must listen to all of them as part of his guilty plea to three counts of criminal sexual\"}, {\"start\": 69.08, \"end\": 71.52, \"text\": \"conduct.\"}, {\"start\": 71.52, \"end\": 78.48, \"text\": \"Earlier this month, another 156 women gave their victim statement in Ingham County, Michigan\"}, {\"start\": 78.48, \"end\": 80.36, \"text\": \"for similar crimes.\"}, {\"start\": 80.36, \"end\": 86.32, \"text\": \"In that case, Nassar was sentenced to up 175 years in prison.\"}, {\"start\": 86.32, \"end\": 93.16, \"text\": \"That's on top of 60 years for federal child pornography charges.\"}, {\"start\": 93.24, \"end\": 98.0, \"text\": \"In the current case, Nassar could be sentenced for up to 125 years in prison.\"}, {\"start\": 98.0, \"end\": 102.16, \"text\": \"His sentences from his two other cases already means he will spend the rest of his life in\"}, {\"start\": 102.36, \"end\": 104.72, \"text\": \"prison.\"}, {\"start\": 106.2, \"end\": 116.16, \"text\": \"At 11:20 Wednesday morning, an Amtrak train carrying several Republican members of Congress\"}, {\"start\": 116.16, \"end\": 118.2, \"text\": \"collided with the truck in Crozet, Virginia.\"}, {\"start\": 118.2, \"end\": 121.24, \"text\": \"In addition to Congress members, their spouses, some family members and aides were on board\"}, {\"start\": 121.24, \"end\": 123.92, \"text\": \"as well.\"}, {\"start\": 124.04, \"end\": 131.8, \"text\": \"They were heading for a retreat in White Sulfur Springs, West Virginia.\"}, {\"start\": 131.84, \"end\": 140.84, \"text\": \"Amtrak officials say the train hit a truck that was straddling the tracks.\"}, {\"start\": 140.84, \"end\": 144.76, \"text\": \"There were three people in the truck.\"}, {\"start\": 144.76, \"end\": 147.08, \"text\": \"The driver of the truck was killed.\"}, {\"start\": 147.08, \"end\": 151.96, \"text\": \"Multiple sources said say that all members of Congress on the train and their families\"}, {\"start\": 152.16, \"end\": 156.68, \"text\": \"were okay, with the exception of a few minor injuries.\"}, {\"start\": 156.68, \"end\": 163.84, \"text\": \"And several Congress members with medical training helped the injured and performed CPR.\"}, {\"start\": 163.92, \"end\": 170.24, \"text\": \"As the National Transportation Safety Board investigated the deadly crash, legislators\"}, {\"start\": 170.4, \"end\": 176.2, \"text\": \"boarded buses and continued on to their destination.\"}, {\"start\": 178.68, \"end\": 184.48, \"text\": \"Last night President Trump laid out his plan for a comprehensive immigration plan, asking\"}, {\"start\": 184.84, \"end\": 198.76, \"text\": \"lawmakers to set aside their differences to seek common ground.\"}, {\"start\": 198.76, \"end\": 206.2, \"text\": \"The president's immigration plan includes a path to citizenship for 1.8 million undocumented\"}, {\"start\": 206.44, \"end\": 216.36, \"text\": \"people who were brought to the country as children, an idea that is unpopular with hardline\"}, {\"start\": 216.36, \"end\": 218.64, \"text\": \"Republicans.\"}, {\"start\": 218.64, \"end\": 222.84, \"text\": \"But Democrats draw the line when it comes to other parts of his plan including major\"}, {\"start\": 222.84, \"end\": 232.64, \"text\": \"changes to the visa lottery system and family-based immigration rules.\"}, {\"start\": 232.72, \"end\": 238.6, \"text\": \"This sets up yet another potential showdown next week, as the government is set to run\"}, {\"start\": 238.8, \"end\": 242.12, \"text\": \"out of money on February 8th.\"}, {\"start\": 242.12, \"end\": 248.12, \"text\": \"As part of the deal to reopen the government last week, leader Mitch McConnell said he\"}, {\"start\": 248.16, \"end\": 253.4, \"text\": \"would hold a vote on protecting dreamers.\"}, {\"start\": 253.4, \"end\": 261.84, \"text\": \"But with opposition from both Republicans and Democrats, it may prove to be too difficult\"}, {\"start\": 261.84, \"end\": 266.92, \"text\": \"for the White House to line up the president's vision with that of Congress.\"}, {\"start\": 269.56, \"end\": 275.88, \"text\": \"The US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) is looking for a new leader.\"}, {\"start\": 275.88, \"end\": 283.56, \"text\": \"CDC director Dr. Brenda Fitzgerald resigned from her position on Wednesday, just six months\"}, {\"start\": 283.76, \"end\": 288.64, \"text\": \"after being selected for the post.\"}, {\"start\": 288.64, \"end\": 296.44, \"text\": \"In a statement, the Department of Health and Human Services says Fitzgerald's \\\"complex\"}, {\"start\": 296.44, \"end\": 298.8, \"text\": \"financial interests\\\" led to her decision.\"}, {\"start\": 298.8, \"end\": 306.28, \"text\": \"The move comes one day after \\\"Politico\\\" reported that Fitzgerald bought tobacco stock after\"}, {\"start\": 306.28, \"end\": 307.76, \"text\": \"becoming CDC director.\"}, {\"start\": 307.76, \"end\": 315.32, \"text\": \"Such an investment goes against the mission of the CDC.\"}, {\"start\": 319.08, \"end\": 328.44, \"text\": \"Many people got a chance to see what NASA is calling a \\\"lunar trifecta,\\\" the super blue\"}, {\"start\": 328.44, \"end\": 332.2, \"text\": \"blood moon.\"}, {\"start\": 332.2, \"end\": 338.36, \"text\": \"Take a look at these amazing images from around the world.\"}, {\"start\": 338.36, \"end\": 342.24, \"text\": \"This full moon is special for three reasons.\"}, {\"start\": 342.4, \"end\": 350.6, \"text\": \"One -- the moon is closer to Earth in its orbit and 14 percent brighter than usual.\"}, {\"start\": 350.72, \"end\": 358.6, \"text\": \"Two -- it's the second full moon of the month, commonly known as a blue moon.\"}, {\"start\": 358.6, \"end\": 365.84, \"text\": \"And finally -- this super blue moon will pass through earth's shadow for a total lunar eclipse.\"}, {\"start\": 365.84, \"end\": 376.04, \"text\": \"While in the Earth's shadow, the moon will take on a reddish tint.\"}, {\"start\": 376.04, \"end\": 379.04, \"text\": \"That's known as a blood moon.\"}, {\"start\": 379.04, \"end\": 387.4, \"text\": \"People living in the West Coast, Alaska or Hawaii, got to see all three before sunrise\"}, {\"start\": 387.4, \"end\": 389.08, \"text\": \"on January 31st.\"}, {\"start\": 390.88, \"end\": 406.2, \"text\": \"Lexus has partnered with Marvel Comics and will release its new Super Bowl commercial\"}, {\"start\": 406.2, \"end\": 415.16, \"text\": \"starring Chadwick Bozeman as Black Panther this Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 415.16, \"end\": 428.28, \"text\": \"It's a 60 second spot for Lexus' L-S 500 F-Sport.\"}, {\"start\": 428.28, \"end\": 442.96, \"text\": \"It's a thrilling chase scene where Black Panther has to recover a stolen ore and make an appearance\"}, {\"start\": 442.96, \"end\": 447.64, \"text\": \"at a leadership conference for his country.\"}, {\"start\": 447.96, \"end\": 450.24, \"text\": \"We have a sneak peek of the commercial.\"}, {\"start\": 450.24, \"end\": 451.56, \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"}, {\"start\": 451.72, \"end\": 456.2, \"text\": \"(engine revs)\"}, {\"start\": 456.2, \"end\": 460.16, \"text\": \"(fighting sounds)\"}, {\"start\": 460.32, \"end\": 462.44, \"text\": \"Vibranium secured.\"}, {\"start\": 462.44, \"end\": 463.72, \"text\": \"Well done my king.\"}, {\"start\": 464.56, \"end\": 466.28, \"text\": \"Is my ride ready?\"}, {\"start\": 466.28, \"end\": 469.0, \"text\": \"Of course big brother, but you have to hurry.\"}, {\"start\": 470.16, \"end\": 471.28, \"text\": \"(music) Step into the spotlight!\"}, {\"start\": 471.28, \"end\": 472.72, \"text\": \"(music) Whoo!\"}, {\"start\": 474.12, \"end\": 475.6, \"text\": \"(music) Whoo!\"}, {\"start\": 476.88, \"end\": 478.48, \"text\": \"(music) And the crowd goes...\"}, {\"start\": 478.88, \"end\": 479.84, \"text\": \"(music) And the crowd goes..\"}, {\"start\": 480.0, \"end\": 483.44, \"text\": \"(music) And the crowd goes...Whoo!\"}, {\"start\": 485.28, \"end\": 486.08, \"text\": \"Show off!\"}, {\"start\": 486.4, \"end\": 487.04, \"text\": \"(music) Whoo!\"}, {\"start\": 489.44, \"end\": 491.52, \"text\": \"(music) Step into the spotlight! Whoo!\"}, {\"start\": 494.48, \"end\": 496.0, \"text\": \"(music) Whoo!\"}, {\"start\": 496.64, \"end\": 500.08, \"text\": \"(Announcer) Experience luxury performance it takes the crown.\"}, {\"start\": 500.4, \"end\": 503.04, \"text\": \"Presenting the all new Lexus LS 500.\"}, {\"start\": 503.76, \"end\": 508.56, \"text\": \"Long live the king.\"}, {\"start\": 512.56, \"end\": 515.2, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 515.2, \"end\": 516.88, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 516.88, \"end\": 519.84, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 519.84, \"end\": 524.4, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 524.4, \"end\": 532.24, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "O7361D4IHWA": {
    "video_id": "O7361D4IHWA",
    "title": "FCC recommends 3-digit number for suicide hotline (ASL - 8.17.19)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20190817",
    "duration": 87,
    "view_count": 68,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.28, \"end\": 16.12, \"text\": \"The Federal Communications Commission is recommending that Congress designate a three-digit\"}, {\"start\": 16.56, \"end\": 19.92, \"text\": \"number for the National Suicide Prevention Hotline.\"}, {\"start\": 19.92, \"end\": 31.96, \"text\": \"The FCC recommends the use of the digits 988 because it's a shorter number and easier to remember.\"}, {\"start\": 31.96, \"end\": 47.6, \"text\": \"Currently calls to the 11-digit suicide hotline number are routed to the closest certified crisis center.\"}, {\"start\": 47.6, \"end\": 54.76, \"text\": \"That number is 1-800-273-TALK (8255).\"}, {\"start\": 54.76, \"end\": 68.68, \"text\": \"Last year, counselors with the hotline answered over 2.2 million calls and over 100,000 online chats.\"}, {\"start\": 68.68, \"end\": 76.6, \"text\": \"If you are Deaf, there is a national hotline in the US, Canada, the UK and England.\"}, {\"start\": 76.6, \"end\": 78.52, \"text\": \"It's available 24/7 and it's free.\"}, {\"start\": 78.52, \"end\": 83.96, \"text\": \"Just text \\\"DEAF 741 741.\\\"\"}]"
  },
  "gRt8imZfprY": {
    "video_id": "gRt8imZfprY",
    "title": "Obamas tweet Valentine's Day love messages to each other (ASL - 2.14.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180215",
    "duration": 71,
    "view_count": 113,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.94, \"end\": 17.06, \"text\": \"Former First Lady Michelle Obama tweeted: “Happy #Valentine’s Day to my one and\"}, {\"start\": 17.06, \"end\": 19.48, \"text\": \"only, @Barack Obama.\"}, {\"start\": 19.48, \"end\": 26.5, \"text\": \"To celebrate the occasion, I’m dedicating a little Valentine’s Day playlist to you!”\"}, {\"start\": 26.5, \"end\": 41.4, \"text\": \"The playlist includes songs such as “Fallin’ by Alicia Keys, “Halo” by Beyoncé and\"}, {\"start\": 41.4, \"end\": 53.96, \"text\": \"“Just The Way You Are” by Billy Joel.\"}, {\"start\": 53.96, \"end\": 62.42, \"text\": \"Former President Barack Obama also honored his wife on Valentine’s Day tweeting: “She\"}, {\"start\": 62.42, \"end\": 69.54, \"text\": \"makes every day and every place better.”\"}]"
  },
  "ZsboUVmjCp0": {
    "video_id": "ZsboUVmjCp0",
    "title": "Screw in boy's skull, millimeter away from death (ASL 1.27.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180127",
    "duration": 84,
    "view_count": 190,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.04, \"end\": 15.0, \"text\": \"Thirteen-year-old Darius Foreman is recovery after a brush with death last weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 15.0, \"end\": 30.52, \"text\": \"Last Saturday, the Maryland boy was building a tree house when he fell from a branch and\"}, {\"start\": 30.52, \"end\": 32.2, \"text\": \"knocked over a wooden board that had a 6-inch screw in it.\"}, {\"start\": 32.2, \"end\": 36.72, \"text\": \"The board slammed down on his head and thrust the screw into his skull.\"}, {\"start\": 36.72, \"end\": 47.72, \"text\": \"First responders had to cut the board from 5-feet to 2-feet in order to get Darius into\"}, {\"start\": 47.88, \"end\": 50.32, \"text\": \"the ambulance.\"}, {\"start\": 50.32, \"end\": 59.72, \"text\": \"His mother says the rest of the board remained attached to his head for about seven hours.\"}, {\"start\": 59.72, \"end\": 70.52, \"text\": \"Doctors say he was just a millimeter away from bleeding to death.\"}, {\"start\": 70.52, \"end\": 80.72, \"text\": \"Darius is now recovering from a successful surgery and says he is going to keep the screw\"}, {\"start\": 80.72, \"end\": 83.08, \"text\": \"that nearly ended his life.\"}]"
  },
  "rg0aNrsRMVc": {
    "video_id": "rg0aNrsRMVc",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.17.20",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200318",
    "duration": 882,
    "view_count": 1675,
    "description": "-COVID-19 vaccine trial administers first dose to participant\n-Asymptomatic people could be driving virus spread \n-Can your pet contract coronavirus?\n-Most airlines could be bankrupt by May\n-Dollar General to hold senior shopper hour\n-Universal to put current movies on demand",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.72, \"end\": 8.3, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.3, \"end\": 12.88, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 12.88, \"end\": 14.72, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 14.72, \"end\": 20.02, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 25.96, \"end\": 36.74, \"text\": \"There has been an important first step in finding a safe and effective vaccine for covid-19.\"}, {\"start\": 36.74, \"end\": 49.22, \"text\": \"A participant in a coronavirus vaccine trial in the US has been administered their first dose.\"}, {\"start\": 49.24, \"end\": 58.16, \"text\": \"The National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases is funding the trial and made the\"}, {\"start\": 58.16, \"end\": 60.5, \"text\": \"announcement Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 60.5, \"end\": 73.96, \"text\": \"The trial is run out of the Kaiser Permanente Washington Health Research Institute in Seattle.\"}, {\"start\": 73.96, \"end\": 82.82, \"text\": \"The study aims to enroll a total of 45 healthy adults over a six week time frame.\"}, {\"start\": 82.82, \"end\": 95.32, \"text\": \"Each participant will receive two injections about a month apart in varying doses.\"}, {\"start\": 95.32, \"end\": 108.24, \"text\": \"The study is meant to prove that the vaccine is safe and to induce a desired response from\"}, {\"start\": 108.24, \"end\": 112.58, \"text\": \"participants immune systems.\"}, {\"start\": 112.58, \"end\": 124.26, \"text\": \"However experts say proving the vaccine is effective in preventing covid-19 infection\"}, {\"start\": 124.26, \"end\": 132.8, \"text\": \"will require follow-up studies involving many more participants.\"}, {\"start\": 132.8, \"end\": 142.8, \"text\": \"And that could take many more months.\"}, {\"start\": 145.88, \"end\": 155.5, \"text\": \"As the coronavirus death toll mounts, now there are questions arising about whether\"}, {\"start\": 155.5, \"end\": 163.4, \"text\": \"US officials might have gotten it wrong about how the virus spreads.\"}, {\"start\": 163.4, \"end\": 176.08, \"text\": \"On March 1, Secretary of Health and Human Services Alex Azar said on ABC's This Week\"}, {\"start\": 176.1, \"end\": 184.18, \"text\": \"that it's mainly spread by people who already sick.\"}, {\"start\": 184.18, \"end\": 194.12, \"text\": \"The website for the Centers for Disease Control said the same thing.\"}, {\"start\": 194.14, \"end\": 213.36, \"text\": \"Now the question is: \\\"Can someone spread the virus without being sick?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 213.36, \"end\": 234.02, \"text\": \"The answer now from the CDC: \\\"Some spread might be possible before people show symptoms\"}, {\"start\": 234.02, \"end\": 244.82, \"text\": \"but this is not thought to be the main way the virus spreads.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 244.82, \"end\": 255.74, \"text\": \"But in Massachusetts more than 80 people contracted coronavirus at a conference held by a biotech company.\"}, {\"start\": 255.74, \"end\": 266.64, \"text\": \"The State Department of Public Health told CNN that none of the people who attended displayed\"}, {\"start\": 266.64, \"end\": 273.32, \"text\": \"any symptoms during the conference.\"}, {\"start\": 273.32, \"end\": 288.0, \"text\": \"Epidemiologists say this is evidence the virus is being transmitted to people who show no\"}, {\"start\": 288.0, \"end\": 302.76, \"text\": \"symptoms of coronavirus and that makes the outbreak even more difficult to control.\"}, {\"start\": 302.76, \"end\": 310.74, \"text\": \"There are no statistics that point to the percentage of people who are getting infected\"}, {\"start\": 310.74, \"end\": 322.9, \"text\": \"with the virus by people who don't have symptoms.\"}, {\"start\": 322.9, \"end\": 331.84, \"text\": \"However on Saturday Doctor Deborah Birx, the coordinator of the White House coronavirus\"}, {\"start\": 331.84, \"end\": 342.3, \"text\": \"response task force, sent a somewhat different message, suggesting that people under age\"}, {\"start\": 342.3, \"end\": 353.98, \"text\": \"20 could possibly be spreading the virus without having any symptoms.\"}, {\"start\": 353.98, \"end\": 365.88, \"text\": \"And many health experts say that means it's time to have a serious discussion about this\"}, {\"start\": 365.88, \"end\": 384.14, \"text\": \"virus that might be spreading in ways they had not anticipated.\"}, {\"start\": 385.28, \"end\": 393.3, \"text\": \"A lot of things are changing in our day-to-day lives at this moment and people all over the\"}, {\"start\": 393.3, \"end\": 400.06, \"text\": \"globe are looking for ways keep their families healthy and safe.\"}, {\"start\": 400.06, \"end\": 404.06, \"text\": \"But what about our pets?\"}, {\"start\": 404.06, \"end\": 414.92, \"text\": \"There's a lot of misinformation floating around about whether pets can contract coronavirus.\"}, {\"start\": 414.94, \"end\": 422.82, \"text\": \"Multiple health organizations have already stated that pets and animals are not at risk\"}, {\"start\": 422.82, \"end\": 425.52, \"text\": \"of contracting covid-19.\"}, {\"start\": 425.52, \"end\": 433.2, \"text\": \"However they can carry the virus on there fur.\"}, {\"start\": 433.2, \"end\": 445.48, \"text\": \"The American Veterinary Medical Association (AVMA) says it's very unlikely a person would\"}, {\"start\": 445.48, \"end\": 461.74, \"text\": \"contract the virus by petting or playing with their pets but make sure you bathe your pets\"}, {\"start\": 461.74, \"end\": 464.78, \"text\": \"and wash your hands after petting them.\"}, {\"start\": 464.8, \"end\": 474.74, \"text\": \"The AVMA also advises people who have contracted novel coronavirus to limit interactions with\"}, {\"start\": 474.74, \"end\": 480.34, \"text\": \"their pets out of an abundance of caution.\"}, {\"start\": 480.34, \"end\": 493.76, \"text\": \"For example if you walk your dog you may want to figure out alternative routes that are\"}, {\"start\": 493.76, \"end\": 499.96, \"text\": \"not populated with many people.\"}, {\"start\": 502.62, \"end\": 512.54, \"text\": \"The coronavirus is making the airline industry so sick many major carriers may go bankrupt.\"}, {\"start\": 512.54, \"end\": 522.94, \"text\": \"One consulting group is projecting most airlines in the world will be out of money by the end of May.\"}, {\"start\": 522.94, \"end\": 534.88, \"text\": \"Europe's biggest low-cost carrier Ryanair said on Monday it will ground most of its\"}, {\"start\": 534.88, \"end\": 539.6, \"text\": \"fleet over the next 7 to 10 days.\"}, {\"start\": 539.6, \"end\": 554.08, \"text\": \"That follows the biggest cutback by Delta in its history and United Airlines cut its capacity in half.\"}, {\"start\": 554.08, \"end\": 562.64, \"text\": \"The three major airline alliances joined forces Monday calling for government help.\"}, {\"start\": 562.64, \"end\": 580.62, \"text\": \"OneWorld, SkyTeam and Star Alliance together represent nearly 60 airlines.\"}, {\"start\": 580.62, \"end\": 592.88, \"text\": \"One of their demands is asking airport operators to waive fees like landing charges.\"}, {\"start\": 592.88, \"end\": 607.66, \"text\": \"However airport operators are also losing revenue from the downturn in air traffic and\"}, {\"start\": 607.66, \"end\": 612.6, \"text\": \"may need help themselves.\"}, {\"start\": 612.6, \"end\": 618.06, \"text\": \"According to an airline industry group, airlines plan to request a $50 billion aid package\"}, {\"start\": 618.08, \"end\": 621.14, \"text\": \"from the US government.\"}, {\"start\": 621.14, \"end\": 629.8, \"text\": \"But even with government bailouts, industry observers believe some airlines will continue\"}, {\"start\": 629.8, \"end\": 637.98, \"text\": \"to face financial problems.\"}, {\"start\": 643.7, \"end\": 652.86, \"text\": \"As retailers adjust to the coronavirus pandemic, Dollar General is accommodating seniors.\"}, {\"start\": 652.86, \"end\": 666.68, \"text\": \"The retailer says it will let seniors shop by themselves for the first hour each day.\"}, {\"start\": 666.68, \"end\": 674.84, \"text\": \"Older adults are at a higher risk of developing complications from covid-19.\"}, {\"start\": 674.86, \"end\": 685.86, \"text\": \"And many seniors are on fixed incomes.\"}, {\"start\": 685.86, \"end\": 693.54, \"text\": \"So a safer way to shop at a discount store might be an appealing option to them.\"}, {\"start\": 693.54, \"end\": 702.34, \"text\": \"Dollar General says it will also change its hours.\"}, {\"start\": 702.34, \"end\": 711.68, \"text\": \"That's because health officials are urging people to stay home to stop the spread of coronavirus.\"}, {\"start\": 711.68, \"end\": 716.8, \"text\": \"The new schedule started Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 720.48, \"end\": 737.28, \"text\": \"Thanks to Universal Pictures you can now see the latest movies in theaters without leaving your home.\"}, {\"start\": 737.28, \"end\": 744.16, \"text\": \"On Monday the studio announced it will make three of its newest films available for streaming\"}, {\"start\": 744.16, \"end\": 745.62, \"text\": \"this week.\"}, {\"start\": 745.62, \"end\": 762.54, \"text\": \"\\\"The Invisible Man,\\\" \\\"The Hunt\\\" and \\\"Emma\\\" are currently playing in movie theaters nationwide.\"}, {\"start\": 762.54, \"end\": 771.72, \"text\": \"Universal says starting Friday the movies can also be rented from on-demand services\"}, {\"start\": 771.72, \"end\": 778.5, \"text\": \"offered by Comcast, Apple, Amazon and Sky.\"}, {\"start\": 778.5, \"end\": 786.42, \"text\": \"The movies will cost around $20 each and can be rented for 48 hours.\"}, {\"start\": 786.42, \"end\": 798.36, \"text\": \"DreamWorks animation, a subsidiary of Universal, is also making its movies \\\"Trolls World Tour\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 798.36, \"end\": 802.1, \"text\": \"available for on-demand starting next month.\"}, {\"start\": 802.1, \"end\": 812.4, \"text\": \"The movie is slated to go online April 10, the same day it's expected to hit theaters.\"}, {\"start\": 814.68, \"end\": 817.7, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 817.7, \"end\": 821.04, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 821.04, \"end\": 825.64, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 825.64, \"end\": 833.42, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms.\"}]"
  },
  "2bXnkd7DGc8": {
    "video_id": "2bXnkd7DGc8",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.12.2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171213",
    "duration": 444,
    "view_count": 420,
    "description": "December 12, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-GLIMMER OF HOPE IN CALIFORINA WILDFIRES\n-FEMALE DEMOCRATIC LAWMAKERS CALL FOR TRUMP INVESTIGATION\n-TRUMP VS GILLIBRAND TWITTER WAR\n-DEPUTY CATCHES INMATE WHO JUMPS FROM 2ND FLOOR\n-HISTORIC 2018 WINTER OLYMPICS\n-CUSTOMER LEAVES $2,000 TIP\n-GIRL SCOUT COOKIE-FLAVORED YOGURT\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE Our talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have back",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.26, \"end\": 9.76, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.78, \"end\": 10.96, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.04, \"end\": 13.32, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.42, \"end\": 21.52, \"text\": \"Historic wildfires have made the landscape in California look like hell on earth over\"}, {\"start\": 21.52, \"end\": 24.92, \"text\": \"the past week.\"}, {\"start\": 24.98, \"end\": 28.46, \"text\": \"Six major wildfires are torching the state.\"}, {\"start\": 28.46, \"end\": 37.18, \"text\": \"Together they have engulfed an area larger than the cities of Boston and New York combined.\"}, {\"start\": 37.26, \"end\": 45.9, \"text\": \"The flames have destroyed thousands of structures, hundreds of thousands of acres have been scorched\"}, {\"start\": 45.98, \"end\": 50.22, \"text\": \"and nearly 100,000 people have been forced to evacuate.\"}, {\"start\": 50.3, \"end\": 56.3, \"text\": \"The cost of fighting the blaze is already in the tens of millions of dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 56.36, \"end\": 66.18, \"text\": \"But firefighters say there is a glimmer of hope.\"}, {\"start\": 66.18, \"end\": 72.52, \"text\": \"As of Monday evening they had contained roughly 20% of the flames.\"}, {\"start\": 72.56, \"end\": 78.82, \"text\": \"And although winds of 20 to 40 mph are expected through midweek\"}, {\"start\": 78.88, \"end\": 83.96, \"text\": \"it's an improvement over the powerful wind gust that fanned the flames in previous days.\"}, {\"start\": 86.18, \"end\": 93.84, \"text\": \"More than 50 female Democratic lawmakers are calling on Congress to investigate allegations\"}, {\"start\": 93.84, \"end\": 99.76, \"text\": \"of sexual misconduct against President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 99.84, \"end\": 106.76, \"text\": \"Today the Democratic Women's Working Group held a press conference demanding President\"}, {\"start\": 106.76, \"end\": 111.08, \"text\": \"Trump be held accountable for his actions.\"}, {\"start\": 111.14, \"end\": 117.92, \"text\": \"Thirteen women have come forward accusing the president of sexual assault --\"}, {\"start\": 117.92, \"end\": 122.4, \"text\": \"accusations the president has repeatedly denied.\"}, {\"start\": 122.5, \"end\": 139.74, \"text\": \"Senator Kirsten Gillibrand joins Democrats Cory Booker, Jeff Merkley and Ron Wyden --\"}, {\"start\": 139.74, \"end\": 145.16, \"text\": \"calling for Trump to step down.\"}, {\"start\": 147.04, \"end\": 155.82, \"text\": \"Senator Kirsten Gillibrand and President Trump got into a twitter war over her calls for\"}, {\"start\": 155.82, \"end\": 160.14, \"text\": \"him to step down.\"}, {\"start\": 160.22, \"end\": 165.66, \"text\": \"Trump tweeted this:\"}, {\"start\": 165.72, \"end\": 176.4, \"text\": \"\\\"Lightweight Sen. Kirsten Gillibrand, a total flunky for Chuck Schumer and someone who would\"}, {\"start\": 176.46, \"end\": 185.58, \"text\": \"come to my office begging for campaign contributions not so long ago and would do anything for\"}, {\"start\": 185.58, \"end\": 188.82, \"text\": \"them, is now in the ring fighting against Trump.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 188.94, \"end\": 192.7, \"text\": \"Gillibrand responded to the twitter attack.\"}, {\"start\": 192.76, \"end\": 196.08, \"text\": \"She said this:\"}, {\"start\": 196.08, \"end\": 201.98, \"text\": \"\\\"You cannot silence me or the millions of women who have gotten off the sidelines to\"}, {\"start\": 202.04, \"end\": 207.7, \"text\": \"speak out about the unfitness and shame you have brought to the Oval office.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 207.78, \"end\": 215.04, \"text\": \"When a reporter asked Trump to clarify his tweet about Gillibrand,\"}, {\"start\": 215.04, \"end\": 218.32, \"text\": \"Trump walked out of the room without responding.\"}, {\"start\": 220.18, \"end\": 228.6, \"text\": \"Deputies at a Nye County Detention Center in Nevada are being credited\"}, {\"start\": 228.62, \"end\": 233.68, \"text\": \"with saving an inmate who jumped from the second floor balcony.\"}, {\"start\": 233.68, \"end\": 241.76, \"text\": \"We have the video that shows the inmate climbing over the railing.\"}, {\"start\": 241.86, \"end\": 245.32, \"text\": \"One deputy runs up the stairs to try to stop him.\"}, {\"start\": 245.42, \"end\": 246.84, \"text\": \"But the inmate manages to jump anyway.\"}, {\"start\": 246.96, \"end\": 251.44, \"text\": \"Another deputy, watching from below, caught him -- cushioning his fall.\"}, {\"start\": 251.52, \"end\": 253.92, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 265.94, \"end\": 273.54, \"text\": \"The deputy and inmate were taken to the hospital to be checked out but neither was hurt.\"}, {\"start\": 273.54, \"end\": 280.98, \"text\": \"Officials at Nye County Detention Center say the inmate was suicidal.\"}, {\"start\": 283.5, \"end\": 290.36, \"text\": \"The 2018 Winter Olympics in Pyeongchang is getting off to a historic start.\"}, {\"start\": 290.36, \"end\": 297.62, \"text\": \"First -- a robot has taken part of the torch relay for the first time in Olympic history.\"}, {\"start\": 297.62, \"end\": 302.5, \"text\": \"It served as an opportunity to promote Korea's advanced robotics technology to the world\"}, {\"start\": 302.52, \"end\": 305.24, \"text\": \"and also heat up the Olympics fever.\"}, {\"start\": 305.3, \"end\": 311.76, \"text\": \"Second -- Nigeria will be represented at the Winter Olympics game for the first time ever.\"}, {\"start\": 311.78, \"end\": 317.06, \"text\": \"The country's women's team qualified for the bobsled.\"}, {\"start\": 317.08, \"end\": 318.96, \"text\": \"Congratulations ladies!\"}, {\"start\": 319.0, \"end\": 324.6, \"text\": \"The 2018 Winter Olympics start on February 9 and end February 25.\"}, {\"start\": 327.04, \"end\": 335.54, \"text\": \"Christmas came early at an Arizona diner -- thanks to a very generous customer.\"}, {\"start\": 335.54, \"end\": 340.18, \"text\": \"Employers say a man came in and ordered bacon and eggs.\"}, {\"start\": 340.18, \"end\": 349.1, \"text\": \"The breakfast cost $17 but when the man left, he left behind a $2,000 tip.\"}, {\"start\": 349.1, \"end\": 355.72, \"text\": \"A note on the receipt asked that the money be split among the entire diner staff.\"}, {\"start\": 355.72, \"end\": 362.5, \"text\": \"During a hectic holiday season, it was a welcome early gift for nine lucky employees.\"}, {\"start\": 362.5, \"end\": 368.7, \"text\": \"Employees say the \\\"Secret Santa\\\" act of kindness seems to be contagious.\"}, {\"start\": 368.7, \"end\": 373.48, \"text\": \"Another employee reportedly received a $200 tip.\"}, {\"start\": 375.42, \"end\": 380.42, \"text\": \"Have you ever wanted the taste of Girl Scout cookies in your yogurt?\"}, {\"start\": 380.42, \"end\": 382.22, \"text\": \"Well, now is your chance!\"}, {\"start\": 382.32, \"end\": 389.0, \"text\": \"Yoplait is announcing three new flavors inspired by Girl Scout cookies.\"}, {\"start\": 389.0, \"end\": 399.06, \"text\": \"They are thin mints, carmel coconut and peanut butter chocolate.\"}, {\"start\": 399.12, \"end\": 408.74, \"text\": \"The flavors are also gluten-free and contain no high fructose corn syrup.\"}, {\"start\": 408.74, \"end\": 416.7, \"text\": \"Yoplait says all three yogurts will be available at stores nationwide beginning this month.\"}, {\"start\": 416.7, \"end\": 419.36, \"text\": \"After that, they will be available all year round.\"}, {\"start\": 421.1, \"end\": 423.12, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 423.2, \"end\": 424.6, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 424.64, \"end\": 426.4, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 426.48, \"end\": 430.86, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 430.86, \"end\": 436.18, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-o9Tj5gJGI4": {
    "video_id": "-o9Tj5gJGI4",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.18.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180419",
    "duration": 399,
    "view_count": 1357,
    "description": "4.18.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Southwest pilot praised for \"nerves of steel\"\n-Puerto Rico suffers island-wide power outage\n-Tributes pour in for Barbara Bush\n-Trump & Abe talk trade, prep for meeting with N. Korea\n-New surveillance video of \"Gambling Grandma\"\n-FDA issues caffeine warning\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable orga",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.7, \"end\": 9.08, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.08, \"end\": 11.24, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.24, \"end\": 12.56, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 12.56, \"end\": 16.04, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.14, \"end\": 28.54, \"text\": \"Yesterday an engine on a Southwest Airline blew apart in midflight and broke a window.\"}, {\"start\": 28.54, \"end\": 37.6, \"text\": \"Several passengers were injured and one passenger died from her injuries after being partially\"}, {\"start\": 37.64, \"end\": 40.48, \"text\": \"pulled out of the aircraft.\"}, {\"start\": 40.48, \"end\": 48.38, \"text\": \"But passengers on board are praising the pilot Tammy Jo Shults for her calm demeanor and\"}, {\"start\": 48.38, \"end\": 52.32, \"text\": \"superb aviation skills.\"}, {\"start\": 52.38, \"end\": 58.04, \"text\": \"She managed to land the plane safely and spoke to each passenger directly after the landing\"}, {\"start\": 58.04, \"end\": 63.64, \"text\": \"to make sure everyone was all right.\"}, {\"start\": 66.38, \"end\": 73.24, \"text\": \"The citizens of Puerto Rico can't catch a break.\"}, {\"start\": 73.32, \"end\": 81.84, \"text\": \"Today the power authority said the entire island is without power.\"}, {\"start\": 81.84, \"end\": 87.96, \"text\": \"The cause of the blackout is unclear.\"}, {\"start\": 87.96, \"end\": 96.8, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico had already been dealing with unstable power ever since hurricane Maria\"}, {\"start\": 96.8, \"end\": 104.1, \"text\": \"slammed into the island last year and destroyed the electrical grid.\"}, {\"start\": 104.1, \"end\": 111.92, \"text\": \"Officials are hoping power will be restored within the next 24 to 36 hours.\"}, {\"start\": 112.72, \"end\": 122.46, \"text\": \"Former first lady Barbara Bush died yesterday at the age of 92.\"}, {\"start\": 122.46, \"end\": 131.48, \"text\": \"As a result, flags around the country and the world flew at half-staff in her memory\"}, {\"start\": 131.48, \"end\": 138.12, \"text\": \"and tributes and condolences poured in, including at the White House, where people left messages\"}, {\"start\": 138.12, \"end\": 139.7, \"text\": \"in a condolences book.\"}, {\"start\": 139.7, \"end\": 146.42, \"text\": \"She was one of only two women in American history to be both a wife and mother of a\"}, {\"start\": 146.42, \"end\": 150.2, \"text\": \"US president.\"}, {\"start\": 150.2, \"end\": 156.56, \"text\": \"Bush was diagnosed with Graves' disease in the 1980s and also had congestive heart failure\"}, {\"start\": 156.64, \"end\": 160.7, \"text\": \"and COPD, which affects the lungs.\"}, {\"start\": 163.76, \"end\": 181.14, \"text\": \"President Trump and Japanese prime minister Shinto Abe were at Mar-a-Lago today continuing\"}, {\"start\": 181.14, \"end\": 190.74, \"text\": \"their discussions on trade and possibly a critical meeting with North Korea's leader\"}, {\"start\": 190.74, \"end\": 195.94, \"text\": \"Kim Jong-Un.\"}, {\"start\": 195.94, \"end\": 207.0, \"text\": \"Trump says he has a healthy relationship with Abe but the current trade deal between the\"}, {\"start\": 207.0, \"end\": 216.38, \"text\": \"two countries is not bilateral and needs to be amended immediately.\"}, {\"start\": 216.38, \"end\": 232.84, \"text\": \"We also learned CIA director Mike Pompeo met with Kim Jong-Un during the Easter holiday\"}, {\"start\": 232.84, \"end\": 236.76, \"text\": \"and more talks might take place soon.\"}, {\"start\": 236.76, \"end\": 247.76, \"text\": \"A White House official says Kim Jong-Un was personable and well prepared during the talks\"}, {\"start\": 247.76, \"end\": 251.1, \"text\": \"with Pompeo.\"}, {\"start\": 254.44, \"end\": 262.76, \"text\": \"Earlier this week we told you about a nationwide manhunt for the woman seen in this video.\"}, {\"start\": 262.76, \"end\": 272.04, \"text\": \"Her name is Lois Riess and she is accused of killing her husband and a woman in Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 272.04, \"end\": 285.16, \"text\": \"Police released this new video of Riess driving the dead woman's car to a hotel in Ocala,\"}, {\"start\": 285.16, \"end\": 294.88, \"text\": \"Florida, then calmly walking through the hotel and up to the registration counter.\"}, {\"start\": 294.88, \"end\": 304.24, \"text\": \"The US marshals service is offering a $5,000 reward for information leading to her arrest\"}, {\"start\": 304.24, \"end\": 311.74, \"text\": \"and Florida Crimestoppers is also offering a reward of up to $1,000.\"}, {\"start\": 314.56, \"end\": 320.82, \"text\": \"The FDA is warning consumers to stay away from powder\"}, {\"start\": 320.82, \"end\": 334.96, \"text\": \"and liquid dietary supplements with high concentrations of caffeine.\"}, {\"start\": 334.96, \"end\": 343.84, \"text\": \"The FDA says some of these products can contain as much as 3,200 mg of caffeine, the equivalent\"}, {\"start\": 343.84, \"end\": 350.28, \"text\": \"of 28 cups of coffee, which can be fatal.\"}, {\"start\": 350.28, \"end\": 356.88, \"text\": \"In fact two deaths have already been linked to high caffeine supplements.\"}, {\"start\": 356.88, \"end\": 363.64, \"text\": \"The FDA is also trying to get these products removed from store shelves.\"}, {\"start\": 368.72, \"end\": 371.6, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 371.6, \"end\": 373.08, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 373.08, \"end\": 376.16, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 376.16, \"end\": 382.4, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 382.4, \"end\": 385.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 385.0, \"end\": 386.92, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 386.92, \"end\": 389.72, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "nJnr_thzg0c": {
    "video_id": "nJnr_thzg0c",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.27.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180428",
    "duration": 345,
    "view_count": 1178,
    "description": "4.27.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-North and South Korea discuss denuclearization\n-Tennessee Waffle House hero raises money for the victims\n-Five African American women are asked to leave PA golf course\n-Janelle Monáe talks about her sexuality\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN, FOX,",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.96, \"end\": 9.58, \"text\": \"Hello everyone!\"}, {\"start\": 9.58, \"end\": 12.6, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.6, \"end\": 14.8, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 14.8, \"end\": 19.2, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for the day.\"}, {\"start\": 21.28, \"end\": 32.88, \"text\": \"North and South Korea say they have agreed to declare the Korean War over in 2018.\"}, {\"start\": 32.88, \"end\": 42.88, \"text\": \"It's the first time the leaders of the two Koreas have met in more than a decade.\"}, {\"start\": 42.88, \"end\": 52.4, \"text\": \"And it is the first time a North Korean leader has set foot onto South Korea since 1953.\"}, {\"start\": 52.4, \"end\": 54.16, \"text\": \"It's a historic event.\"}, {\"start\": 54.16, \"end\": 64.72, \"text\": \"The leaders of North and South Korea met face-to-face to improve relations on the Korean Peninsula.\"}, {\"start\": 64.72, \"end\": 74.0, \"text\": \"South Korea wants denuclearization and peace between the two countries.\"}, {\"start\": 74.0, \"end\": 85.28, \"text\": \"A few months ago the U.S. and North Korea appeared to be on the brink of war.\"}, {\"start\": 85.28, \"end\": 93.84, \"text\": \"But now it's possible that President Trump will meet with the North Korean leader later this year.\"}, {\"start\": 96.72, \"end\": 106.56, \"text\": \"James Shaw Junior is being called a hero.\"}, {\"start\": 106.56, \"end\": 120.72, \"text\": \"Shaw grabbed a rifle from Travis Reinking who opened fire at a Tennessee Waffle House.\"}, {\"start\": 120.72, \"end\": 138.48, \"text\": \"Shaw was inside the restaurant when the gunman entered and ambushed the gunman when\"}, {\"start\": 138.48, \"end\": 144.96, \"text\": \"he wasn't looking.\"}, {\"start\": 145.04, \"end\": 154.4, \"text\": \"Now Shaw has started a fundraiser for families of the victims.\"}, {\"start\": 154.4, \"end\": 161.52, \"text\": \"Almost $171,000 has been donated.\"}, {\"start\": 164.56, \"end\": 175.44, \"text\": \"Five African-American women say the manager at Grandview Golf Course in Pennsylvania\"}, {\"start\": 175.44, \"end\": 181.84, \"text\": \"called the cops because they were golfing too slow.\"}, {\"start\": 181.84, \"end\": 190.24, \"text\": \"The women didn't think they were playing slower than anyone else.\"}, {\"start\": 190.24, \"end\": 196.08, \"text\": \"Another golfer waiting behind them agreed.\"}, {\"start\": 196.08, \"end\": 200.96, \"text\": \"But the manager called 911 anyway.\"}, {\"start\": 200.96, \"end\": 209.04, \"text\": \"When the police came, the manager said the women sped up their game.\"}, {\"start\": 209.04, \"end\": 216.64, \"text\": \"But he later said they were still too slow.\"}, {\"start\": 216.64, \"end\": 221.28, \"text\": \"The police decided it was not a police matter and left.\"}, {\"start\": 221.28, \"end\": 229.36, \"text\": \"Later the five women left on their own and no charges were filed.\"}, {\"start\": 229.36, \"end\": 236.16, \"text\": \"The next day the owner of the golf course apologized to the women.\"}, {\"start\": 236.16, \"end\": 241.2, \"text\": \"However, the women said they won't be going back to the golf course again.\"}, {\"start\": 241.2, \"end\": 249.44, \"text\": \"They said they felt discriminated against as both women and minorities.\"}, {\"start\": 255.2, \"end\": 270.88, \"text\": \"Recently singer and actress Janelle Monae talked about her sexual orientation.\"}, {\"start\": 270.88, \"end\": 282.48, \"text\": \"In a Rolling Stones cover story Monae called herself a \\\"black queer woman.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 282.48, \"end\": 287.12, \"text\": \"And said she's had relationships with men and women.\"}, {\"start\": 287.12, \"end\": 294.64, \"text\": \"Monae says she references women as love interests in many of her songs.\"}, {\"start\": 294.64, \"end\": 304.4, \"text\": \"She said she hopes her songs inspire anyone struggling with acceptance.\"}, {\"start\": 304.4, \"end\": 314.24, \"text\": \"Her new album, \\\"Dirty Computer,\\\" debuts today.\"}, {\"start\": 316.32, \"end\": 319.76, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 319.76, \"end\": 321.44, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 321.44, \"end\": 324.08, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 324.08, \"end\": 329.68, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 329.68, \"end\": 332.56, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 332.56, \"end\": 334.0, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 334.0, \"end\": 339.36, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "o0vCRLF-0Uk": {
    "video_id": "o0vCRLF-0Uk",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.15.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171216",
    "duration": 411,
    "view_count": 485,
    "description": "December 15, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-MURDER CHARGE UPGRADE FOR CHARLOTTESVILLE SUSPECT\n-SECURITY COUNCIL MEETING REGARDING N. KOREA\n-TRUMP ADDRESSES GRADUATES AT FBI ACADEMY\n-DUSTIN HOFFMAN FACES NEW SEXUAL ASSAULT ALLEGATIONS\n-OBAMACARE ENROLLMENT DEADLINE\n-PRINCE HARRY & MEGHAN MARKLE SET WEDDING DATE\n-\"STORMY\" THE COW ESCAPES...AGAIN!\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE Our talented staff works hard each day to deliver qua",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.78, \"end\": 8.64, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.7, \"end\": 10.46, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.52, \"end\": 11.62, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 11.68, \"end\": 13.92, \"text\": \"Here your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.6, \"end\": 26.92, \"text\": \"Twenty-year-old James Alex Fields, Junior is now facing a first-degree murder charge.\"}, {\"start\": 26.96, \"end\": 45.68, \"text\": \"Fields is accused of ramming his car into a crowd during a white nationalist rally in\"}, {\"start\": 45.68, \"end\": 49.82, \"text\": \"Charlottesville, Virginia on August 12th.\"}, {\"start\": 49.86, \"end\": 55.42, \"text\": \"Charlottesville resident Heather Heyer was killed in the crash.\"}, {\"start\": 55.42, \"end\": 57.8, \"text\": \"Dozens of others were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 57.82, \"end\": 70.32, \"text\": \"Fields was originally charged with second-degree murder along with other offenses.\"}, {\"start\": 70.36, \"end\": 83.6, \"text\": \"Fields' case will next be presented to a grand jury in order to get an indictment.\"}, {\"start\": 85.2, \"end\": 93.06, \"text\": \"The United Nations Security Council held a meeting on Friday regarding North Korea.\"}, {\"start\": 93.06, \"end\": 98.5, \"text\": \"The meeting included North Korea's representative to the UN.\"}, {\"start\": 98.52, \"end\": 105.62, \"text\": \"At the meeting world diplomats called on North Korea to end his provocations and abide by\"}, {\"start\": 105.66, \"end\": 109.64, \"text\": \"the non-proliferation rules of the international community -- which are designed to prevent\"}, {\"start\": 109.66, \"end\": 114.84, \"text\": \"the spread of nuclear weapons and weapons technology.\"}, {\"start\": 114.84, \"end\": 120.78, \"text\": \"In response, North Korea said its nuclear program is to defend its sovereignty\"}, {\"start\": 120.82, \"end\": 124.06, \"text\": \"and territorial integrity.\"}, {\"start\": 125.08, \"end\": 131.88, \"text\": \"Today President Trump addressed graduates at the FBI National Academy.\"}, {\"start\": 131.88, \"end\": 139.02, \"text\": \"The ceremony was for state, local and international law enforcement trainees.\"}, {\"start\": 139.02, \"end\": 144.74, \"text\": \"The president praised the graduates and pledged his support for them.\"}, {\"start\": 144.82, \"end\": 151.9, \"text\": \"He said with him as president, America's police will have a true friend\"}, {\"start\": 151.9, \"end\": 153.92, \"text\": \"and loyal companion in the White House.\"}, {\"start\": 153.94, \"end\": 163.04, \"text\": \"However last week Trump slammed the FBI for what he called \\\"very, very disgraceful actions.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 164.08, \"end\": 176.0, \"text\": \"Five women are accusing actor Dustin Hoffman of sexual harassment or sexual assault.\"}, {\"start\": 176.0, \"end\": 191.48, \"text\": \"According to Variety, the two-time Oscar-winner exposed himself to a teenage girl in 1980.\"}, {\"start\": 191.48, \"end\": 200.26, \"text\": \"Hoffman is also accused of assaulting two women in 1987.\"}, {\"start\": 200.26, \"end\": 211.12, \"text\": \"A woman named Pauline tells the Hollywood Reporter Hoffman masturbated in front of her\"}, {\"start\": 211.12, \"end\": 216.22, \"text\": \"in the early 70s when she was 15.\"}, {\"start\": 216.22, \"end\": 226.0, \"text\": \"Another woman said Hoffman forced her to perform oral sex when she was 21 during the period\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 233.28, \"text\": \"the actor shot the movie \\\"All The President's Men.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 233.28, \"end\": 239.42, \"text\": \"Hoffman has not commented on the allegations.\"}, {\"start\": 240.52, \"end\": 246.28, \"text\": \"If you haven't signed up for healthcare coverage under the affordable care act --\"}, {\"start\": 246.28, \"end\": 247.98, \"text\": \"time is running out.\"}, {\"start\": 248.06, \"end\": 254.06, \"text\": \"Today is the last day to sign up to ensure insurance coverage for 2018.\"}, {\"start\": 254.06, \"end\": 260.24, \"text\": \"You have until 11:59 PM tonight to enroll in a plan.\"}, {\"start\": 260.28, \"end\": 266.5, \"text\": \"People affected by the hurricanes can get an extension,\"}, {\"start\": 266.5, \"end\": 273.28, \"text\": \"but you need to check to make sure that you qualify.\"}, {\"start\": 273.32, \"end\": 280.58, \"text\": \"Go to the website healthcare.gov to find out.\"}, {\"start\": 280.64, \"end\": 287.56, \"text\": \"States that run their own insurance marketplaces are\"}, {\"start\": 287.64, \"end\": 290.86, \"text\": \"expected to continue enrollment through January.\"}, {\"start\": 292.1, \"end\": 297.92, \"text\": \"A date has been set for the highly anticipated royal wedding between\"}, {\"start\": 297.98, \"end\": 304.7, \"text\": \"Prince Harry and Meghan Markle.\"}, {\"start\": 304.7, \"end\": 317.36, \"text\": \"Kensington Palace announced on Friday Harry and Megan will marry on May 19, 2018.\"}, {\"start\": 317.44, \"end\": 327.02, \"text\": \"The Palace had said earlier the wedding would be in May in St. George's Chapel,\"}, {\"start\": 327.02, \"end\": 331.12, \"text\": \"Windsor Castle.\"}, {\"start\": 332.36, \"end\": 350.08, \"text\": \"\\\"Stormy\\\" the cow's escaped from a live nativity scene in Philadelphia -- for the second time.\"}, {\"start\": 350.16, \"end\": 356.8, \"text\": \"The scene is on display at the Old First Reformed United Church of Christ.\"}, {\"start\": 356.8, \"end\": 362.96, \"text\": \"Each time \\\"Stormy\\\" escapes, police have to wrangle her back in.\"}, {\"start\": 363.04, \"end\": 368.64, \"text\": \"Stormy's owner says she must have figured out how to push the gate open\"}, {\"start\": 368.8, \"end\": 371.36, \"text\": \"and now she's playing with it.\"}, {\"start\": 371.52, \"end\": 379.2, \"text\": \"Unfortunately Stormy's live performing days are over for now.\"}, {\"start\": 379.2, \"end\": 387.52, \"text\": \"She has been sent back to the farm and replaced with her younger daughter \\\"Ginger.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 388.72, \"end\": 390.24, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 390.32, \"end\": 391.28, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 391.28, \"end\": 393.28, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 393.28, \"end\": 397.36, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 397.6, \"end\": 402.88, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "rCxgHVKgntg": {
    "video_id": "rCxgHVKgntg",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.24.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180125",
    "duration": 612,
    "view_count": 1926,
    "description": "1.24.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Nassar sentenced to 175 years in prison\n-Protests over Trump visit to Davos\n-Zainab Ansari killer caught\n-Stoplight shootout caught on camera\n-Tiffany Haddish signs deal with HBO\n-Cereal boxes transform into simple machines\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provi",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 9.7, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.7, \"end\": 12.32, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.32, \"end\": 13.4, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.4, \"end\": 16.5, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.98, \"end\": 29.38, \"text\": \"Former USA gymnastics doctor Larry Nassar will spend the rest of his life behind bars.\"}, {\"start\": 29.38, \"end\": 42.86, \"text\": \"Today a Michigan judge sentenced him to 40 to 175 years in prison for sexual assault.\"}, {\"start\": 42.86, \"end\": 51.76, \"text\": \"That's in addition to the 60 years in federal prison he will serve for child pornography.\"}, {\"start\": 51.76, \"end\": 60.16, \"text\": \"After handing down her sentence, the judge said to Nassar \\\"I just signed your death warrant.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 60.16, \"end\": 70.18, \"text\": \"People in the courtroom started cheering and hugging when Nassar was taken away.\"}, {\"start\": 70.18, \"end\": 77.38, \"text\": \"But his legal battles are far from over.\"}, {\"start\": 77.38, \"end\": 86.34, \"text\": \"Now an investigation into his former employer, Michigan State, is underway.\"}, {\"start\": 86.34, \"end\": 93.8, \"text\": \"Nassar worked for the school for decades and treated hundreds of athletes.\"}, {\"start\": 93.8, \"end\": 100.56, \"text\": \"Officials with the NCAA are looking into possible rules violations in connection to Nassar's\"}, {\"start\": 100.56, \"end\": 102.16, \"text\": \"assaults.\"}, {\"start\": 102.16, \"end\": 111.48, \"text\": \"Protesters are also calling on university president Lou Anna Simon to resign.\"}, {\"start\": 114.38, \"end\": 130.92, \"text\": \"President Trump is taking his \\\"America First\\\" message to the world economic forum in Davos,\"}, {\"start\": 130.92, \"end\": 132.28, \"text\": \"Switzerland this week.\"}, {\"start\": 132.28, \"end\": 146.96, \"text\": \"However thousands of people marched through Zurich and other major Swiss cities to demonstrate\"}, {\"start\": 146.96, \"end\": 149.94, \"text\": \"against Trump's visit.\"}, {\"start\": 149.94, \"end\": 159.7, \"text\": \"Leaders from France, Germany and Italy will address the forum Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 159.76, \"end\": 163.78, \"text\": \"And Trump will give his keynote address on Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 163.78, \"end\": 174.68, \"text\": \"The forum brings together leaders from all over the world to discuss free-trade and international\"}, {\"start\": 174.68, \"end\": 176.66, \"text\": \"cooperation.\"}, {\"start\": 176.66, \"end\": 189.36, \"text\": \"President Trump is the first US president to attend the summit in almost 20 years.\"}, {\"start\": 191.98, \"end\": 200.24, \"text\": \"Pakistani police say a 24-year old man, identified only as \\\"Imran\\\", is believed to have killed and murdered\"}, {\"start\": 200.24, \"end\": 207.9, \"text\": \"Zainab Ansari earlier this month.\"}, {\"start\": 208.0, \"end\": 217.44, \"text\": \"Zainab is a seven-year-old who was tortured, strangled, raped and thrown into a pile of\"}, {\"start\": 217.48, \"end\": 220.76, \"text\": \"trash.\"}, {\"start\": 220.76, \"end\": 225.44, \"text\": \"Pakistani officials believe Imran is a serial killer\"}, {\"start\": 225.44, \"end\": 233.88, \"text\": \"who raped and murdered several young girls.\"}, {\"start\": 233.88, \"end\": 250.46, \"text\": \"Officials say Imran's DNA matched samples found on Zainab's body, which was dumped about\"}, {\"start\": 250.46, \"end\": 252.16, \"text\": \"300 feet from her home.\"}, {\"start\": 254.44, \"end\": 269.34, \"text\": \"Police in Pensacola, Florida are searching for a man involved in a shoot out at a stoplight.\"}, {\"start\": 269.34, \"end\": 283.56, \"text\": \"It happened around noon on Monday at the intersection of Fairfield Drive and W. Street.\"}, {\"start\": 283.66, \"end\": 300.14, \"text\": \"Police say the driver of a silver Lexus pulled up at a stoplight and exchanged gunfire with\"}, {\"start\": 300.14, \"end\": 304.14, \"text\": \"someone in a gold Toyota.\"}, {\"start\": 304.14, \"end\": 306.64, \"text\": \"And it was all caught on camera.\"}, {\"start\": 306.64, \"end\": 307.9, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 327.999, \"end\": 337.029, \"text\": \"There were two children in the Toyota but amazingly no one was hurt in the shootout.\"}, {\"start\": 337.029, \"end\": 344.22, \"text\": \"Police later spotted the Toyota and arrested the suspect after a brief chase.\"}, {\"start\": 344.22, \"end\": 349.24, \"text\": \"But they are still looking for the driver of the Lexus.\"}, {\"start\": 349.28, \"end\": 358.36, \"text\": \"It has a Florida tag number H-V-R-G-6-9.\"}, {\"start\": 358.36, \"end\": 371.12, \"text\": \"Anyone with information on the shooting is asked to call the Escambia County Sheriff's\"}, {\"start\": 371.12, \"end\": 387.14, \"text\": \"office at 850-436-9620 or Crimestoppers at 850-433-7867.\"}, {\"start\": 388.98, \"end\": 400.22, \"text\": \"According to Variety magazine, actress and comedian Tiffany Haddish has signed a two-year\"}, {\"start\": 400.22, \"end\": 405.7, \"text\": \"deal to develop new projects for HBO.\"}, {\"start\": 405.7, \"end\": 421.6, \"text\": \"It's a \\\"first look\\\" deal, which means HBO gets to accept or reject Haddish's new show\"}, {\"start\": 421.6, \"end\": 426.56, \"text\": \"ideas before other networks.\"}, {\"start\": 426.56, \"end\": 434.3, \"text\": \"No word on how much the deal is worth.\"}, {\"start\": 434.3, \"end\": 442.42, \"text\": \"Haddish runs her own production company called \\\"She Ready.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 442.42, \"end\": 455.78, \"text\": \"She also won the \\\"New York Film Critics Circle\\\" best supporting actress award for her role\"}, {\"start\": 455.78, \"end\": 460.28, \"text\": \"in the film \\\"Girl's Trip\\\" last year.\"}, {\"start\": 460.3, \"end\": 473.1, \"text\": \"Her book \\\"The Last Black Unicorn\\\" was released\"}, {\"start\": 473.1, \"end\": 479.68, \"text\": \"month and became a New York Times bestseller.\"}, {\"start\": 479.68, \"end\": 490.56, \"text\": \"Haddish's upcoming projects include a television series with Tracy Morgan and a film with Kevin\"}, {\"start\": 490.56, \"end\": 494.96, \"text\": \"Hart.\"}, {\"start\": 494.96, \"end\": 504.24, \"text\": \"She will spend some of 2018 on the road touring her standup comedy act.\"}, {\"start\": 507.2, \"end\": 524.48, \"text\": \"General Mills has partnered with Rube Goldberg, Inc. to put out cereal boxes that can be transformed\"}, {\"start\": 524.48, \"end\": 526.32, \"text\": \"into simple machines.\"}, {\"start\": 526.32, \"end\": 542.0, \"text\": \"The specially marked boxes include Cheerios, Cinnamon Toast Crunch, Coco Puffs, Cookie\"}, {\"start\": 542.0, \"end\": 549.839, \"text\": \"Crisp, Lucky Charms and Reese's Puffs.\"}, {\"start\": 549.84, \"end\": 559.2, \"text\": \"Each box includes fun and easy instructions that promote science, technology, engineering\"}, {\"start\": 559.2, \"end\": 561.6, \"text\": \"and math education.\"}, {\"start\": 561.6, \"end\": 575.1, \"text\": \"If you post a picture of your machine on Instagram or the General Mills cereal Facebook page,\"}, {\"start\": 575.1, \"end\": 578.24, \"text\": \"you could qualify for a chance to win a college scholarship.\"}, {\"start\": 581.3, \"end\": 585.82, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 585.82, \"end\": 587.38, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 587.38, \"end\": 590.4, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 590.4, \"end\": 595.98, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 596.02, \"end\": 603.08, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life.Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "6eRl2gkin9w": {
    "video_id": "6eRl2gkin9w",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.31.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171231",
    "duration": 359,
    "view_count": 742,
    "description": "December 31, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Quadruple murder suspects arrested\n-Alabama teen beaten by police, family wants answers\n-Police attacked by a squirrel\n-#MeToo creator to drop NYC New Year’s Eve ball\n-No Powerball winner, jackpot now $440M\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.98, \"end\": 6.62, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.62, \"end\": 8.34, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.38, \"end\": 9.38, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 9.38, \"end\": 11.8, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 13.68, \"end\": 18.96, \"text\": \"On Tuesday police in Troy, New York found four people dead in the basement of an apartment.\"}, {\"start\": 18.96, \"end\": 27.76, \"text\": \"These two men, Justin C. Mann and James W. White, have been arrested for the quadruple\"}, {\"start\": 27.76, \"end\": 29.84, \"text\": \"murder of two women and two children.\"}, {\"start\": 29.84, \"end\": 42.16, \"text\": \"Mann and White are accused of killing 22-year-old Brandi Mells and 36-year old Shanta Myers\"}, {\"start\": 42.32, \"end\": 55.28, \"text\": \"as well as Myers' children Shanise, 5 and Jeremiah, 11.\"}, {\"start\": 55.28, \"end\": 61.76, \"text\": \"The Troy Police Department released these mugshots last night.\"}, {\"start\": 61.76, \"end\": 66.78, \"text\": \"Both men were arraigned in Troy city court Saturday morning and are being held in the\"}, {\"start\": 66.78, \"end\": 68.92, \"text\": \"county jail.\"}, {\"start\": 71.0, \"end\": 77.26, \"text\": \"We want to warn you that some of the pictures in this story are graphic.\"}, {\"start\": 77.26, \"end\": 87.14, \"text\": \"These are pictures of Alabama teenager Ulysses Wilkerson.\"}, {\"start\": 87.16, \"end\": 93.84, \"text\": \"You can see the bloody white sheet beneath his head.\"}, {\"start\": 93.84, \"end\": 98.84, \"text\": \"His nose, lips and left eye are all swollen.\"}, {\"start\": 98.84, \"end\": 106.06, \"text\": \"Ulysses' mother claims officers assaulted her son while he was in handcuffs.\"}, {\"start\": 106.06, \"end\": 108.78, \"text\": \"The pictures were taken in the hospital after he was arrested.\"}, {\"start\": 108.78, \"end\": 121.5, \"text\": \"According to a press release, officers saw Ulysses walking out from behind a downtown\"}, {\"start\": 121.5, \"end\": 124.3, \"text\": \"business late Sunday night.\"}, {\"start\": 124.3, \"end\": 130.94, \"text\": \"And as officers approached, Ulysses fled and gave chase.\"}, {\"start\": 130.94, \"end\": 136.2, \"text\": \"When they finally apprehended the teen, police said he resisted arrest and refused to comply\"}, {\"start\": 136.2, \"end\": 139.98, \"text\": \"with commands.\"}, {\"start\": 139.98, \"end\": 147.54, \"text\": \"Police say the force they used was reasonable and necessary.\"}, {\"start\": 147.58, \"end\": 154.86, \"text\": \"But Ulysses' family says these pictures say otherwise and they are demanding the officers\"}, {\"start\": 154.86, \"end\": 160.16, \"text\": \"involved in the case be held accountable.\"}, {\"start\": 162.28, \"end\": 169.52, \"text\": \"An overexcited squirrel gave police in Brockport, New York quite a welcome.\"}, {\"start\": 169.56, \"end\": 176.18, \"text\": \"Officers responded to a call Friday about a squirrel that had broken into a house and\"}, {\"start\": 176.18, \"end\": 179.9, \"text\": \"was reportedly eating cookies in the kitchen.\"}, {\"start\": 179.9, \"end\": 183.66, \"text\": \"When police arrived, the squirrel launched off the counter and landed squarely on one\"}, {\"start\": 183.66, \"end\": 185.62, \"text\": \"of the policemen.\"}, {\"start\": 185.62, \"end\": 190.52, \"text\": \"The little guy was eventually captured and released outside.\"}, {\"start\": 190.52, \"end\": 196.08, \"text\": \"The police officer's body cam captured the entire scene.\"}, {\"start\": 196.08, \"end\": 197.88, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 214.4, \"end\": 217.4, \"text\": \"The officers seemed to get a kick out of it.\"}, {\"start\": 217.4, \"end\": 218.92, \"text\": \"They laughed the entire time and so did the homeowner.\"}, {\"start\": 218.92, \"end\": 222.84, \"text\": \"Luckily, no one was injured -- not even the squirrel.\"}, {\"start\": 226.04, \"end\": 233.06, \"text\": \"Tarana Burke, the woman who helped launch the #METOO movement will be launching Times\"}, {\"start\": 233.06, \"end\": 243.68, \"text\": \"Square's New Year's Eve ball drop tonight.\"}, {\"start\": 243.68, \"end\": 252.58, \"text\": \"Burke is a social activist who, along with actress Alyssa Milano, got the #METOO movement\"}, {\"start\": 252.58, \"end\": 255.4, \"text\": \"going last October.\"}, {\"start\": 255.4, \"end\": 264.06, \"text\": \"It encourages sexual-harassment victims to come forward.\"}, {\"start\": 264.06, \"end\": 273.76, \"text\": \"In a tweet, Burke said \\\"With the new year comes new momentum to fuel this work and we\"}, {\"start\": 273.76, \"end\": 277.52, \"text\": \"won't stop anytime soon.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 279.52, \"end\": 285.26, \"text\": \"There were no winners in Saturday night's Powerball drawing.\"}, {\"start\": 285.26, \"end\": 291.88, \"text\": \"So the jackpot is now up to an estimated $440 million!\"}, {\"start\": 291.88, \"end\": 296.4, \"text\": \"There were several smaller prize winners however.\"}, {\"start\": 296.4, \"end\": 308.8, \"text\": \"In case you missed it, the numbers are: 28-- 36 -- 41 -- 51 -- 58 and a Powerball of\"}, {\"start\": 308.8, \"end\": 311.16, \"text\": \"24.\"}, {\"start\": 311.16, \"end\": 315.88, \"text\": \"The new Powerball drawing is Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 315.88, \"end\": 323.88, \"text\": \"Friday's mega millions drawing also had no big winner.\"}, {\"start\": 323.88, \"end\": 327.0, \"text\": \"That jackpot is now up to $343 million.\"}, {\"start\": 327.0, \"end\": 330.8, \"text\": \"The next mega millions drawing is Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 333.12, \"end\": 335.1, \"text\": \"And those your top stories today.\"}, {\"start\": 335.1, \"end\": 336.2, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 336.2, \"end\": 338.2, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 338.2, \"end\": 342.08, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 342.08, \"end\": 347.1, \"text\": \"Happy new year and be safe. See you in 2018!\"}, {\"start\": 347.1, \"end\": 352.16, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "T3HP-1xZdG8": {
    "video_id": "T3HP-1xZdG8",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.13.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180214",
    "duration": 500,
    "view_count": 1497,
    "description": "2.13.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-DACA negotiations have begun \n-Immigrant calls 911 for help, detained by ICE\n-Powerball winner fights to remain anonymous\n-Snapchat faces backlash over redesign\n-App lets workers complain about company anonymously\n-Health benefits of chocolate \n-Robotic dog opens door\n-Lonely Bolivian water frog seeks mate on Match.com\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.96, \"end\": 8.36, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.36, \"end\": 10.38, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.38, \"end\": 11.74, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 11.74, \"end\": 13.82, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.72, \"end\": 22.88, \"text\": \"The immigration debate is officially underway.\"}, {\"start\": 22.88, \"end\": 27.62, \"text\": \"On Monday night Republicans announced that they would only allow immigration to be debated\"}, {\"start\": 27.62, \"end\": 29.84, \"text\": \"on the Senate floor for one week.\"}, {\"start\": 29.84, \"end\": 38.0, \"text\": \"President Trump has already proposed a path to citizenship for undocumented immigrants\"}, {\"start\": 38.0, \"end\": 45.2, \"text\": \"in exchange for 25 billion dollars for border security, including his long-promised wall.\"}, {\"start\": 45.2, \"end\": 51.96, \"text\": \"A Republican bill includes all of Trump's proposals, in addition to sharp cuts to family-based\"}, {\"start\": 52.0, \"end\": 60.6, \"text\": \"migration, which would end the diversity visa program.\"}, {\"start\": 60.6, \"end\": 65.74, \"text\": \"Democrats are against cuts to family migration and ending the diversity visa program.\"}, {\"start\": 65.74, \"end\": 70.36, \"text\": \"But for any measure to pass, it will take 60 votes, which requires support from both\"}, {\"start\": 70.36, \"end\": 74.6, \"text\": \"Republicans and Democrats -- and they have until March 5th to do it.\"}, {\"start\": 74.62, \"end\": 79.14, \"text\": \"That's the day President Trump has given as a deadline for Congress to come up with a\"}, {\"start\": 79.14, \"end\": 82.3, \"text\": \"solution on DACA.\"}, {\"start\": 85.9, \"end\": 98.56, \"text\": \"Last Thursday Seattle resident Wilson Rodriguez Macarreno saw someone trespassing on his property\"}, {\"start\": 98.56, \"end\": 100.74, \"text\": \"and called 911.\"}, {\"start\": 100.74, \"end\": 107.0, \"text\": \"Police ran Macarreno's ID and discovered he had an outstanding warrant.\"}, {\"start\": 107.0, \"end\": 112.53, \"text\": \"But instead of sending him to jail, officers turned Macarreno over to Immigration and Customs\"}, {\"start\": 112.53, \"end\": 120.9, \"text\": \"Enforcement (ICE) and now he's being held in a detention facility awaiting deportation.\"}, {\"start\": 120.9, \"end\": 124.52, \"text\": \"The police department said officers believed they were executing a valid order from the\"}, {\"start\": 124.52, \"end\": 128.59, \"text\": \"judge in the form of a criminal warrant.\"}, {\"start\": 128.59, \"end\": 138.68, \"text\": \"But immigration advocates say the way authorities handled the case could make immigrants scared\"}, {\"start\": 138.68, \"end\": 142.86, \"text\": \"to report crimes.\"}, {\"start\": 145.54, \"end\": 155.22, \"text\": \"Last month a New Hampshire woman won 560 million dollars in the Powerball lottery but she hasn't\"}, {\"start\": 155.22, \"end\": 157.36, \"text\": \"claim the money yet.\"}, {\"start\": 157.36, \"end\": 164.96, \"text\": \"Today the woman was in court fighting to remain anonymous.\"}, {\"start\": 164.96, \"end\": 176.92, \"text\": \"State lottery rules say she is required to make her name public unless she had a trustee\"}, {\"start\": 176.92, \"end\": 179.459, \"text\": \"sign her winning ticket.\"}, {\"start\": 179.46, \"end\": 194.56, \"text\": \"Her attorney says making her name public could expose her to violence, harassment and scams.\"}, {\"start\": 198.68, \"end\": 209.8, \"text\": \"Last week Snapchat rolled out a redesigned app and users hate it!\"}, {\"start\": 209.8, \"end\": 217.62, \"text\": \"Snapchat previously featured content from friends, publishers and celebrities on one page.\"}, {\"start\": 217.62, \"end\": 224.42, \"text\": \"Now there is a designated page for publishers and page for friends.\"}, {\"start\": 224.42, \"end\": 232.36, \"text\": \"Over 800,000 people signed a Change.org petition to help convince the company to change the\"}, {\"start\": 232.36, \"end\": 235.08, \"text\": \"app back to the basics.\"}, {\"start\": 235.08, \"end\": 240.38, \"text\": \"A Snapchat spokesperson said it's going to take some time for people to get used to the\"}, {\"start\": 240.38, \"end\": 243.14, \"text\": \"new design but hopes users will enjoy it once they settle in.\"}, {\"start\": 245.94, \"end\": 257.28, \"text\": \"An app called \\\"Blind\\\" is helping employees speak up about problems at work -- with anonymity.\"}, {\"start\": 257.28, \"end\": 265.58, \"text\": \"The app first launched in 2014 in South Korea, but since coming to the United States, it\"}, {\"start\": 265.58, \"end\": 273.56, \"text\": \"has added tens of thousands of employee complaints from tech companies like Apple, Amazon and\"}, {\"start\": 273.56, \"end\": 275.5, \"text\": \"Google.\"}, {\"start\": 275.5, \"end\": 283.6, \"text\": \"If you want to sign up, \\\"Blind\\\" requires users to use their company email address but posts\"}, {\"start\": 283.6, \"end\": 287.56, \"text\": \"are not linked back to the user.\"}, {\"start\": 287.56, \"end\": 296.06, \"text\": \"Last month Lyft began investigating complaints after accusations of improper access to rider\"}, {\"start\": 296.06, \"end\": 302.86, \"text\": \"data were posted on \\\"Blind.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 306.72, \"end\": 316.56, \"text\": \"Tomorrow is Valentine's Day and if you don't know what to get your significant other, try\"}, {\"start\": 316.56, \"end\": 318.42, \"text\": \"chocolate.\"}, {\"start\": 318.42, \"end\": 323.0, \"text\": \"It's not only a romantic gift but it also has several health benefits.\"}, {\"start\": 323.0, \"end\": 330.7, \"text\": \"Researchers say a quarter of an ounce of dark chocolate everyday lowers your risk of a heart\"}, {\"start\": 330.7, \"end\": 344.0, \"text\": \"attack or stroke, it helps reduce inflammation in the body and it definitely improves a person's\"}, {\"start\": 344.0, \"end\": 346.62, \"text\": \"mood.\"}, {\"start\": 346.62, \"end\": 351.42, \"text\": \"But remember moderation is the key.\"}, {\"start\": 354.32, \"end\": 366.1, \"text\": \"Researchers at Boston Dynamics released new video of their \\\"Spotmini\\\" dog that can open doors.\"}, {\"start\": 366.12, \"end\": 367.68, \"text\": \"doors.\"}, {\"start\": 367.7, \"end\": 373.5, \"text\": \"Opening doors is a simple feat for humans but it's actually a complex series of steps\"}, {\"start\": 373.5, \"end\": 376.04, \"text\": \"for a robot.\"}, {\"start\": 376.04, \"end\": 386.64, \"text\": \"The video shows a \\\"Spotmini\\\" outfitted with a robotic arm opening the door for another\"}, {\"start\": 386.64, \"end\": 390.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Spotmini\\\" dog.\"}, {\"start\": 390.0, \"end\": 391.6, \"text\": \"It's pretty cool.  Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 422.08, \"end\": 430.4, \"text\": \"A frog named Romeo is looking for a mate on Match.com!\"}, {\"start\": 430.4, \"end\": 441.8, \"text\": \"The 11-year-old Bolivian water frog is trying to save his species.\"}, {\"start\": 441.8, \"end\": 450.54, \"text\": \"Researchers say Romeo has been looking for a mate for the past decade with no luck.\"}, {\"start\": 450.54, \"end\": 457.86, \"text\": \"So Match.com has started a fund raising campaign to help Romeo find a mate.\"}, {\"start\": 457.86, \"end\": 462.08, \"text\": \"The goal is to raise 15-thousand dollars before Valentine's Day for 10 trips to places where\"}, {\"start\": 462.08, \"end\": 468.88, \"text\": \"Romeo's species was once common.\"}, {\"start\": 472.22, \"end\": 475.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 475.0, \"end\": 476.36, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 476.36, \"end\": 479.14, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 479.14, \"end\": 484.54, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 484.54, \"end\": 492.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "48lMs6U5n0w": {
    "video_id": "48lMs6U5n0w",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.25.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171026",
    "duration": 571,
    "view_count": 266,
    "description": "October 25, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-FLAKE FALLOUT\n-TRUMP RESPONDS TO FLAKE'S RESIGNATION\n-GEORGE H.W. BUSH RESPONDS TO SEXUAL ASSAULT ALLEGATIONS\n-MICHIGAN TEENS DENIED BOND \n-HIV-POSITIVE SCHOOL AIDE ACCUSED OF SEXUAL ASSAULT\n-FORMER DEPUTY SLAMS INTO EX-WIFE'S HOUSE \n-AMAZON KEY LETS DELIVERY PEOPLE INSIDE YOUR HOUSE\n-SMILING CHIHUAHUA GOES VIRAL\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day t",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.0, \"end\": 23.0, \"text\": \"The political world is still talking about what happened\"}, {\"start\": 23.0, \"end\": 27.0, \"text\": \"last night on the Senate floor. In a stunning speech\"}, {\"start\": 28.0, \"end\": 32.0, \"text\": \"Arizona Senator Jeff Flake announced that he would\"}, {\"start\": 32.0, \"end\": 36.0, \"text\": \"not seek reelection.\"}, {\"start\": 37.0, \"end\": 42.0, \"text\": \"And then he added harsh comments about the leader of his own party\"}, {\"start\": 42.0, \"end\": 45.0, \"text\": \"president Trump. In his speech Flake said he'd had enough.\"}, {\"start\": 45.0, \"end\": 50.0, \"text\": \"He had hoped after nine months of the Trump presidency things would turn around.\"}, {\"start\": 51.0, \"end\": 55.0, \"text\": \"But he said it has not. He believes if Trump keeps running\"}, {\"start\": 55.0, \"end\": 59.0, \"text\": \"the country the way he has, it has the potential for real damage\"}, {\"start\": 59.1, \"end\": 64.1, \"text\": \"to the economy, global politics and foreign relations.\"}, {\"start\": 65.0, \"end\": 69.0, \"text\": \"Flake said a number of his colleagues  feel the same way\"}, {\"start\": 69.0, \"end\": 73.0, \"text\": \"and that in the coming months more people will\"}, {\"start\": 73.024, \"end\": 76.024, \"text\": \"stand up and speak out.\"}, {\"start\": 79.0, \"end\": 83.0, \"text\": \"President Trump went on Twitter to respond to\"}, {\"start\": 83.0, \"end\": 87.0, \"text\": \"Senator Flake's comments. His first tweet said\"}, {\"start\": 88.0, \"end\": 93.0, \"text\": \"Jeff Flake, with an 18 percent\"}, {\"start\": 93.0, \"end\": 98.0, \"text\": \"approval rating in Arizona, said a lot of my\"}, {\"start\": 98.0, \"end\": 103.0, \"text\": \"colleagues have spoken out. Really?\"}, {\"start\": 103.0, \"end\": 108.0, \"text\": \"They just gave me a standing ovation.\"}, {\"start\": 108.0, \"end\": 113.0, \"text\": \"In his second tweet he said the reason\"}, {\"start\": 113.0, \"end\": 118.0, \"text\": \"Flake and Corker dropped out of the Senate race is\"}, {\"start\": 118.0, \"end\": 122.0, \"text\": \"because they had zero chance of becoming elected.\"}, {\"start\": 123.0, \"end\": 126.0, \"text\": \"Now act so hurt and wounded.\"}, {\"start\": 127.0, \"end\": 132.0, \"text\": \"Corker is the former Republican senator from Tennessee\"}, {\"start\": 132.0, \"end\": 136.0, \"text\": \"who has also openly criticized Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 140.0, \"end\": 144.0, \"text\": \"Actress Heather Lind has come forward\"}, {\"start\": 144.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"and accused former President George H.W.\"}, {\"start\": 149.0, \"end\": 155.0, \"text\": \"Bush of sexually assaulting her.\"}, {\"start\": 155.0, \"end\": 158.0, \"text\": \"She says the incident happened a few years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 159.0, \"end\": 162.0, \"text\": \"She says while the former president was sitting in a wheelchair\"}, {\"start\": 162.024, \"end\": 164.024, \"text\": \"he touched her inappropriately\"}, {\"start\": 165.0, \"end\": 171.0, \"text\": \"and told dirty jokes while they were posing for pictures.\"}, {\"start\": 171.0, \"end\": 177.0, \"text\": \"Lind says Mrs. Bush was standing right there.\"}, {\"start\": 177.0, \"end\": 182.0, \"text\": \"Today a spokesperson for the former president issued a statement about\"}, {\"start\": 182.0, \"end\": 187.0, \"text\": \"the allegations. It said President Bush would\"}, {\"start\": 187.0, \"end\": 191.0, \"text\": \"never under any circumstances intentionally cause any one\"}, {\"start\": 191.0, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"distress and he most sincerely apologizes if his\"}, {\"start\": 196.0, \"end\": 201.0, \"text\": \"attempt at humor offended Ms Lind.\"}, {\"start\": 205.024, \"end\": 207.999, \"text\": \"Yesterday a judge denied bond for\"}, {\"start\": 208.0, \"end\": 213.0, \"text\": \"five Michigan teenagers.\"}, {\"start\": 215.0, \"end\": 218.0, \"text\": \"They are accused of\"}, {\"start\": 218.0, \"end\": 225.0, \"text\": \"throwing rocks off a highway overpass.\"}, {\"start\": 227.0, \"end\": 232.0, \"text\": \"Kenneth White was a passenger in a\"}, {\"start\": 232.0, \"end\": 237.0, \"text\": \"van riding home from work when\"}, {\"start\": 237.0, \"end\": 242.0, \"text\": \"a rock crashed through the windshield\"}, {\"start\": 242.0, \"end\": 246.0, \"text\": \"and struck White in the face, head and chest and killed him.\"}, {\"start\": 248.0, \"end\": 251.0, \"text\": \"All five teenagers are being charged\"}, {\"start\": 251.0, \"end\": 258.0, \"text\": \"as adults with one count of second degree murder each.\"}, {\"start\": 259.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"If they're found guilty\"}, {\"start\": 262.0, \"end\": 268.0, \"text\": \"the maximum penalty is life in prison.\"}, {\"start\": 272.024, \"end\": 274.999, \"text\": \"A former Maryland school aide and\"}, {\"start\": 275.0, \"end\": 280.0, \"text\": \"track coach named Carlos\"}, {\"start\": 280.0, \"end\": 285.0, \"text\": \"DeAngelo Bell is accused of\"}, {\"start\": 285.0, \"end\": 291.0, \"text\": \"sexually assaulting 42 students and recording the act.\"}, {\"start\": 291.0, \"end\": 295.0, \"text\": \"According to state lawyers all of the victims\"}, {\"start\": 295.0, \"end\": 300.0, \"text\": \"ranged in age from 11 to 17 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 300.0, \"end\": 305.0, \"text\": \"The alleged abuse spanned from May 2015 to June 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 305.0, \"end\": 311.0, \"text\": \"Bell also admitted he is HIV positive.\"}, {\"start\": 311.0, \"end\": 314.0, \"text\": \"Investigators are not aware of any alleged victims\"}, {\"start\": 314.0, \"end\": 318.0, \"text\": \"testing positive for HIV.\"}, {\"start\": 319.0, \"end\": 325.0, \"text\": \"Now Bell is facing 206 charges.\"}, {\"start\": 325.0, \"end\": 328.0, \"text\": \"If he is found guilty\"}, {\"start\": 329.0, \"end\": 332.0, \"text\": \"he could spend the rest of his life in prison.\"}, {\"start\": 335.024, \"end\": 337.999, \"text\": \"Check out this dramatic dash cam video.\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 343.0, \"text\": \"It's from the inside of former sheriff deputy's\"}, {\"start\": 343.0, \"end\": 347.0, \"text\": \"Tim Taylor's car.\"}, {\"start\": 348.0, \"end\": 352.0, \"text\": \"Last year in Milton Florida\"}, {\"start\": 352.0, \"end\": 356.0, \"text\": \"Deputy Taylor reversed his car out of his ex-wife's driveway.\"}, {\"start\": 356.0, \"end\": 361.0, \"text\": \"Taylor let a car pass and then accelerates the car\"}, {\"start\": 361.024, \"end\": 364.024, \"text\": \"and slams it into the front of the house.\"}, {\"start\": 366.0, \"end\": 369.0, \"text\": \"Taylor admitted he was under the influence\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 373.0, \"text\": \"of prescription drugs at the time. He said he tried to\"}, {\"start\": 373.0, \"end\": 376.0, \"text\": \"commit suicide because of marital problems.\"}, {\"start\": 377.0, \"end\": 383.0, \"text\": \"Taylor pleaded no contest to\"}, {\"start\": 384.0, \"end\": 392.0, \"text\": \"DUI and criminal mischief charges.\"}, {\"start\": 393.0, \"end\": 397.0, \"text\": \"He was sentenced to two years probation.\"}, {\"start\": 403.024, \"end\": 405.024, \"text\": \"Amazon is launching a new service\"}, {\"start\": 405.1, \"end\": 410.0, \"text\": \"called Amazon Key.\"}, {\"start\": 410.0, \"end\": 414.0, \"text\": \"It lets delivery drivers into your home\"}, {\"start\": 414.024, \"end\": 421.024, \"text\": \"when you're not there.\"}, {\"start\": 422.025, \"end\": 423.399, \"text\": \"Starting next month\"}, {\"start\": 424.0, \"end\": 428.0, \"text\": \"Amazon Key will be available in 37 cities around the U.S.\"}, {\"start\": 429.0, \"end\": 434.0, \"text\": \"Prime members will be able to have packages dropped\"}, {\"start\": 434.0, \"end\": 436.0, \"text\": \"just inside their front door\"}, {\"start\": 436.001, \"end\": 440.099, \"text\": \"instead of on the front porch in view of would-be thieves.\"}, {\"start\": 440.1, \"end\": 442.1, \"text\": \"To use the service\"}, {\"start\": 442.1, \"end\": 446.1, \"text\": \"customers will need to buy an Amazon Key\"}, {\"start\": 446.124, \"end\": 447.999, \"text\": \"in-home kit\"}, {\"start\": 448.0, \"end\": 452.0, \"text\": \"that includes a security camera and compatible smart door lock.\"}, {\"start\": 452.0, \"end\": 456.0, \"text\": \"The kits start at $250.\"}, {\"start\": 457.0, \"end\": 462.0, \"text\": \"A Prime membership will cost another $99 a year.\"}, {\"start\": 467.024, \"end\": 469.024, \"text\": \"Taco Bell\"}, {\"start\": 469.1, \"end\": 474.1, \"text\": \"is testing out a new dessert. It's similar to a quesadilla.\"}, {\"start\": 475.0, \"end\": 480.0, \"text\": \"But instead of melted cheese it has a kit kat bar\"}, {\"start\": 480.0, \"end\": 488.0, \"text\": \"melted inside. The company calls it Chocoladilla\"}, {\"start\": 489.0, \"end\": 494.0, \"text\": \"and it costs just one dollar. So far the reaction on social media\"}, {\"start\": 494.0, \"end\": 501.0, \"text\": \"has gone from revulsion to serious interest to sheer excitement.\"}, {\"start\": 504.001, \"end\": 506.999, \"text\": \"Check out this picture.\"}, {\"start\": 507.0, \"end\": 511.0, \"text\": \"It's a picture of a chihuahua that looks like its smiling.\"}, {\"start\": 512.0, \"end\": 518.0, \"text\": \"The dog's name is Cheech and he was at the Waller animal\"}, {\"start\": 518.0, \"end\": 523.0, \"text\": \"shelter in Texas. The workers at the shelter\"}, {\"start\": 523.0, \"end\": 527.0, \"text\": \"posted the picture on Facebook and it went viral.\"}, {\"start\": 528.0, \"end\": 533.0, \"text\": \"Now Cheech has a reason to smile.\"}, {\"start\": 533.0, \"end\": 537.0, \"text\": \"Someone saw the picture, came to the shelter\"}, {\"start\": 537.024, \"end\": 540.924, \"text\": \"and adopted him.\"}, {\"start\": 544.048, \"end\": 546.099, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 546.1, \"end\": 551.0, \"text\": \"I am Jethro Wooddall. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 551.0, \"end\": 555.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 556.0, \"end\": 562.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "IhgMwb1qmGg": {
    "video_id": "IhgMwb1qmGg",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.6.18",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180106",
    "duration": 458,
    "view_count": 782,
    "description": "1.6.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nToday's Headlines:\n-Trump tweets new attack on Wolff and Bannon\n-Australia wants to sell the world marijuana\n-L.A. bakery makes city's largest Kings Cake\n-Blood donors needed\n-Time to clean the refrigerator and freezer\n-One winner in Mega Millions $450 jackpot\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.4, \"end\": 7.06, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.06, \"end\": 8.82, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.82, \"end\": 9.92, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 9.92, \"end\": 12.62, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 13.38, \"end\": 23.9, \"text\": \"President Trump is unleashing a new twitter barrage on Steve Bannon and author Michael\"}, {\"start\": 23.9, \"end\": 26.44, \"text\": \"Wolff.\"}, {\"start\": 26.56, \"end\": 30.76, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 30.76, \"end\": 38.94, \"text\": \"His tweet Friday night said \\\"Michael Wolff is a total loser who made up stories in order\"}, {\"start\": 38.94, \"end\": 44.16, \"text\": \"to sell this really boring and untruthful book.\"}, {\"start\": 44.16, \"end\": 57.24, \"text\": \"He used sloppy Steve Bannon, who cried when he got fired and begged for his job.\"}, {\"start\": 57.24, \"end\": 64.54, \"text\": \"But sloppy Steve has been dumped like a dog by almost everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 64.54, \"end\": 66.54, \"text\": \"Too bad.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 66.54, \"end\": 74.02, \"text\": \"That was a second time in two days that Trump slammed Bannon and Wolff on twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 74.02, \"end\": 84.62, \"text\": \"Wolff's new book \\\"Fire and Fury\\\" portrayed an unflattering picture of Trump as a candidate\"}, {\"start\": 84.62, \"end\": 87.04, \"text\": \"and as a president.\"}, {\"start\": 87.04, \"end\": 94.6, \"text\": \"In his first tweet on Thursday, Trump said the book was \\\"full of lies.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 95.8, \"end\": 102.42, \"text\": \"Earlier this week Australian government officials announced they want the country to become\"}, {\"start\": 102.42, \"end\": 107.04, \"text\": \"the world's number one supplier of medical marijuana.\"}, {\"start\": 107.04, \"end\": 116.9, \"text\": \"Australia legalized medical marijuana at the federal level in 2016 and now it has legalized\"}, {\"start\": 116.9, \"end\": 119.38, \"text\": \"overseas exports.\"}, {\"start\": 119.38, \"end\": 128.2, \"text\": \"Experts say this decision could lead to a big economic boom for Australia.\"}, {\"start\": 128.2, \"end\": 137.04, \"text\": \"The market for medical marijuana could quadruple to a $1 billion industry by 2020.\"}, {\"start\": 137.04, \"end\": 140.8, \"text\": \"Recreational usage of marijuana is still illegal.\"}, {\"start\": 141.92, \"end\": 149.6, \"text\": \"Today is \\\"Three Kings Day\\\" -- a holiday many Christians around the world celebrate.\"}, {\"start\": 149.6, \"end\": 157.6, \"text\": \"One bakery in Los Angeles marked the occasion by making the city's largest \\\"Rosca de Reyes\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 157.6, \"end\": 159.2, \"text\": \"or Kings cake.\"}, {\"start\": 159.2, \"end\": 171.2, \"text\": \"Dozens of people came to try the 24-foot crown cake that took four days to prepare.\"}, {\"start\": 171.2, \"end\": 177.72, \"text\": \"The tradition originated in Spain and became very popular among Latino communities.\"}, {\"start\": 177.72, \"end\": 183.2, \"text\": \"Kings cake will have a small plastic baby inside.\"}, {\"start\": 183.2, \"end\": 186.4, \"text\": \"Their baby represents baby Jesus.\"}, {\"start\": 186.4, \"end\": 193.92, \"text\": \"And the person who gets a piece of cake with the baby is typically responsible for buying\"}, {\"start\": 194.0, \"end\": 198.16, \"text\": \"or making the Kings cake the following year.\"}, {\"start\": 199.12, \"end\": 211.6, \"text\": \"The American Red Cross says someone in the US needs blood every two seconds.\"}, {\"start\": 211.6, \"end\": 218.16, \"text\": \"And right now the American Red Cross is in critical need of O-negative, which is considered\"}, {\"start\": 218.16, \"end\": 220.08, \"text\": \"a universal donor.\"}, {\"start\": 220.08, \"end\": 224.4, \"text\": \"And B-negative because it is so rare.\"}, {\"start\": 224.4, \"end\": 232.52, \"text\": \"If you're considering donating blood, consider these factors when determining if you are\"}, {\"start\": 232.52, \"end\": 236.52, \"text\": \"an eligible donor.\"}, {\"start\": 236.56, \"end\": 241.12, \"text\": \"Whether you're in good general health.\"}, {\"start\": 241.12, \"end\": 248.56, \"text\": \"You have to be at least 17 years old all in most states, 16 years old in others with parental\"}, {\"start\": 248.56, \"end\": 250.8, \"text\": \"consent.\"}, {\"start\": 250.8, \"end\": 254.96, \"text\": \"And weigh at least 110 pounds.\"}, {\"start\": 254.96, \"end\": 259.68, \"text\": \"If you're taking medication, that will not disqualify you as a blood donor in most cases.\"}, {\"start\": 259.68, \"end\": 263.04, \"text\": \"However the reason that you're taking the medication might.\"}, {\"start\": 263.04, \"end\": 269.6, \"text\": \"A short health history and physical evaluation at the donor center or blood drive will determine\"}, {\"start\": 269.6, \"end\": 272.0, \"text\": \"that.\"}, {\"start\": 272.0, \"end\": 276.0, \"text\": \"The process for general donations takes about 8 to 10 minutes and can save a life.\"}, {\"start\": 276.64, \"end\": 281.44, \"text\": \"While you are considering giving yourself a new makeover this new year, think about\"}, {\"start\": 281.44, \"end\": 287.84, \"text\": \"giving one to your refrigerator and freezer too.\"}, {\"start\": 287.84, \"end\": 296.48, \"text\": \"Check out all of the \\\"use by\\\" and expiration dates on dairy products and eggs.\"}, {\"start\": 296.48, \"end\": 300.64, \"text\": \"It may be time to let go of that old block of cheese.\"}, {\"start\": 300.64, \"end\": 304.64, \"text\": \"And throw out that old chip and veggie dip too.\"}, {\"start\": 304.64, \"end\": 315.04, \"text\": \"Some condiments can even become contaminated with bacteria, even if the product says it\"}, {\"start\": 315.04, \"end\": 321.6, \"text\": \"is good for up to six months in the refrigerator.\"}, {\"start\": 321.6, \"end\": 326.72, \"text\": \"Think about everyone in the home using them and how many times they've had their hands\"}, {\"start\": 326.72, \"end\": 331.44, \"text\": \"in the fridge when sick.\"}, {\"start\": 331.44, \"end\": 334.48, \"text\": \"The same goes for the freezer.\"}, {\"start\": 334.48, \"end\": 341.92, \"text\": \"That pint of ice cream you been meaning to get to can go bad after a while.\"}, {\"start\": 341.92, \"end\": 349.68, \"text\": \"And when you clean the fridge, do not use a multi-surface cleaner because you don't\"}, {\"start\": 349.68, \"end\": 355.12, \"text\": \"want your food close to dangerous chemicals.\"}, {\"start\": 355.12, \"end\": 364.64, \"text\": \"Try using vinegar for a cleaning solution to avoid any chemical contamination.\"}, {\"start\": 365.6, \"end\": 372.72, \"text\": \"There was one winner of the massive Mega Millions drawing from Friday night.\"}, {\"start\": 372.72, \"end\": 381.36, \"text\": \"According to the multi-state lottery association, the lucky ticket was bought in Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 381.36, \"end\": 391.52, \"text\": \"The winning numbers were 28, 30, 39, 59, 70 with the Megaball 10.\"}, {\"start\": 391.52, \"end\": 397.12, \"text\": \"The jackpot reached an estimated $450 million.\"}, {\"start\": 397.28, \"end\": 405.36, \"text\": \"That represents the fourth largest amount in Mega Millions history.\"}, {\"start\": 405.36, \"end\": 410.96, \"text\": \"The winner of Friday's Mega Million drawing has not yet been identified.\"}, {\"start\": 410.96, \"end\": 419.36, \"text\": \"Lottery players do have another chance to grab a massive jackpot this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 419.36, \"end\": 428.72, \"text\": \"Tonight is the Powerball drawing with an estimated prize of $570 million.\"}, {\"start\": 428.72, \"end\": 435.04, \"text\": \"That would be the fifth-largest jackpot in that game's history.\"}, {\"start\": 436.8, \"end\": 438.64, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 438.8, \"end\": 440.08, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 440.08, \"end\": 441.84, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 441.92, \"end\": 445.44, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 445.44, \"end\": 450.4, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "EFhz2KRPa68": {
    "video_id": "EFhz2KRPa68",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.24.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171224",
    "duration": 449,
    "view_count": 506,
    "description": "December 24, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-THREE MISS AMERICA LEADERS RESIGN OVER EMAILS\n-GUNMAN KILLED AFTER TARGETING POLICE\n-\"REAL HOUSEWIVES\" STAR ARRESTED\n-POPE FRANCIS DELIVERS CHRISTMAS EVE ANGELUS\n-TRUMP HOLDS TRADITIONAL MILITARY TELECONFERENCE\n-NORAD TO TRACK SANTA ON CHRISTMAS EVE\n-DEAF WOMAN SIGNS \"SANTA CLAUS IS COMING TO TOWN\"\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.44, \"end\": 7.62, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.62, \"end\": 9.72, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.72, \"end\": 10.9, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 10.9, \"end\": 13.18, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.54, \"end\": 19.74, \"text\": \"Three leaders of the Miss America organization are stepping down following allegations they\"}, {\"start\": 19.74, \"end\": 26.68, \"text\": \"shamed former pageant winners in an exchange of emails.\"}, {\"start\": 26.68, \"end\": 34.12, \"text\": \"The emails referenced their weight and private sex lives.\"}, {\"start\": 34.12, \"end\": 42.64, \"text\": \"The organization says that CEO Sam Haskell resigned on Saturday, along with President\"}, {\"start\": 42.64, \"end\": 55.36, \"text\": \"Josh Randle and Board of Directors chairman Lynn Weidner.\"}, {\"start\": 55.36, \"end\": 60.2, \"text\": \"The pageant's leadership came under fire after a report in \\\"Huffington Post\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 60.2, \"end\": 65.2, \"text\": \"earlier this week.\"}, {\"start\": 65.2, \"end\": 70.72, \"text\": \"Dozens of former Miss Americas later called on some leaders to resign.\"}, {\"start\": 70.74, \"end\": 73.36, \"text\": \"Haskell's resignation is effective immediately.\"}, {\"start\": 73.36, \"end\": 78.18, \"text\": \"But Weidner and Randle will stay on for the time being to facilitate a smooth transition\"}, {\"start\": 78.18, \"end\": 80.94, \"text\": \"in leadership.\"}, {\"start\": 82.1, \"end\": 94.6, \"text\": \"51-year-old Ahmed Aminamin el-Mofty was shot and killed by police Friday in Harrisburg,\"}, {\"start\": 94.62, \"end\": 101.24, \"text\": \"Pennsylvania after he fired several times at law enforcement officers throughout the\"}, {\"start\": 101.24, \"end\": 102.24, \"text\": \"city.\"}, {\"start\": 102.24, \"end\": 110.12, \"text\": \"El-Mofty fired at a Capitol police officer and then shot and injured a state trooper.\"}, {\"start\": 110.14, \"end\": 113.54, \"text\": \"Later he used two handguns to open fire on several officers who then returned fire and\"}, {\"start\": 113.54, \"end\": 115.66, \"text\": \"killed him.\"}, {\"start\": 115.72, \"end\": 123.38, \"text\": \"The Department of Homeland Security is calling the incident a terror attack.\"}, {\"start\": 123.38, \"end\": 130.54, \"text\": \"It highlights the Trump administration's concerns with extended family chain migration.\"}, {\"start\": 130.54, \"end\": 135.44, \"text\": \"El-Mofty was reportedly a naturalized US citizen who came to the country on a family-based\"}, {\"start\": 135.56, \"end\": 139.56, \"text\": \"immigration visa.\"}, {\"start\": 143.48, \"end\": 159.94, \"text\": \"\\\"Real Housewives of New York City\\\" star Luann de Lesseps was arrested in Palm Beach, Florida\"}, {\"start\": 159.94, \"end\": 161.73, \"text\": \"early Sunday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 161.73, \"end\": 168.27, \"text\": \"She was charged with drunk and disorderly conduct, resisting arrest and assault on a\"}, {\"start\": 168.27, \"end\": 169.78, \"text\": \"law enforcement officer.\"}, {\"start\": 169.78, \"end\": 175.06, \"text\": \"Authorities say she slammed the door and kicked at police officers.\"}, {\"start\": 175.06, \"end\": 179.64, \"text\": \"Before she was arrested, police say she yelled at them saying \\\"I'm going to kill you all!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 179.64, \"end\": 186.98, \"text\": \"She was release without bond and allowed to go back to New York.\"}, {\"start\": 186.98, \"end\": 191.7, \"text\": \"But she's due back in court on January 25.\"}, {\"start\": 193.42, \"end\": 202.04, \"text\": \"On Sunday Pope Francis prayed for peace during his Christmas Angelus prayer.\"}, {\"start\": 202.04, \"end\": 210.98, \"text\": \"He spoke in the Vatican from his balcony overlooking St. Peter's Square.\"}, {\"start\": 210.98, \"end\": 216.54, \"text\": \"The Pope also prayed for an end to conflict.\"}, {\"start\": 216.54, \"end\": 222.6, \"text\": \"He also prayed for those suffering amid the deadly flooding caused by a tropical storm\"}, {\"start\": 222.6, \"end\": 225.32, \"text\": \"in the Philippines.\"}, {\"start\": 226.72, \"end\": 234.68, \"text\": \"President Trump is back at his estate in Florida for the Christmas holiday.\"}, {\"start\": 234.68, \"end\": 239.66, \"text\": \"But he spent some time Sunday speaking to American service members deployed abroad.\"}, {\"start\": 239.66, \"end\": 242.32, \"text\": \"He addressed troops from all five military branches in a teleconference from Mar-A-Lago.\"}, {\"start\": 242.32, \"end\": 248.66, \"text\": \"He told them that Americans were asking God to watch out for them.\"}, {\"start\": 248.68, \"end\": 258.18, \"text\": \"Trump took questions but only after members of the media were escorted out of the room.\"}, {\"start\": 258.18, \"end\": 265.32, \"text\": \"The Christmas Eve teleconference continues a tradition set by past presidents.\"}, {\"start\": 265.32, \"end\": 269.36, \"text\": \"Trump also held a similar teleconference on Thanksgiving earlier this year.\"}, {\"start\": 270.98, \"end\": 277.66, \"text\": \"North American Aerospace Defense command, better known as NORAD, is charged with protecting\"}, {\"start\": 277.66, \"end\": 281.04, \"text\": \"American airspace.\"}, {\"start\": 281.08, \"end\": 282.54, \"text\": \"But that doesn't mean it can have a little fun.\"}, {\"start\": 282.54, \"end\": 285.58, \"text\": \"NORAD will continue its Christmas tradition of tracking Santa Claus this year.\"}, {\"start\": 285.58, \"end\": 288.88, \"text\": \"The group said in a statement that the public can access its official Santa Tracker starting\"}, {\"start\": 288.88, \"end\": 292.76, \"text\": \"at 2 AM on Christmas Eve day.\"}, {\"start\": 292.76, \"end\": 304.48, \"text\": \"Starting at 6 AM people can call 1-877-HI-NORAD and speak with an actual NORAD tracker.\"}, {\"start\": 304.52, \"end\": 312.36, \"text\": \"They can even track Santa's progress in their cars if they have an On-Star subscription.\"}, {\"start\": 312.44, \"end\": 317.96, \"text\": \"NORAD is also offering Santa-cams that will allow the public to follow St. Nick's journey\"}, {\"start\": 317.96, \"end\": 320.08, \"text\": \"around the world.\"}, {\"start\": 321.6, \"end\": 328.4, \"text\": \"We love it when our Sign1News fans reach out to us and share interesting,\"}, {\"start\": 328.4, \"end\": 331.4, \"text\": \"fun and funny videos.\"}, {\"start\": 331.4, \"end\": 336.76, \"text\": \"This video comes from Dianna and her son Zarek.\"}, {\"start\": 336.88, \"end\": 340.68, \"text\": \"They live in Ontario, California.\"}, {\"start\": 340.68, \"end\": 344.84, \"text\": \"And they just want to remind everyone to be on your best behavior tonight\"}, {\"start\": 344.84, \"end\": 348.56, \"text\": \"because Santa Claus is coming to town.\"}, {\"start\": 349.94, \"end\": 351.4, \"text\": \"You better watch out.\"}, {\"start\": 351.4, \"end\": 352.44, \"text\": \"You better not cry.\"}, {\"start\": 352.48, \"end\": 353.96, \"text\": \"You better watch not pout.\"}, {\"start\": 353.96, \"end\": 355.34, \"text\": \"I'm telling you why.\"}, {\"start\": 355.34, \"end\": 360.98, \"text\": \"Santa Claus is coming to town.\"}, {\"start\": 360.98, \"end\": 362.56, \"text\": \"He's making a list.\"}, {\"start\": 362.56, \"end\": 363.84, \"text\": \"He's checking it twice.\"}, {\"start\": 363.84, \"end\": 366.88, \"text\": \"He's gonna find out who's naughty or nice.\"}, {\"start\": 366.88, \"end\": 372.08, \"text\": \"Santa Claus is coming to town.\"}, {\"start\": 372.08, \"end\": 374.92, \"text\": \"He sees you when you're sleeping.\"}, {\"start\": 374.92, \"end\": 377.92, \"text\": \"He knows when you're awake.\"}, {\"start\": 377.92, \"end\": 381.0, \"text\": \"He knows if you've been bad or good.\"}, {\"start\": 381.0, \"end\": 384.16, \"text\": \"So be good for goodness sake. Oh...!\"}, {\"start\": 384.16, \"end\": 385.36, \"text\": \"You better watch out.\"}, {\"start\": 385.36, \"end\": 386.8, \"text\": \"You better not cry.\"}, {\"start\": 386.8, \"end\": 388.24, \"text\": \"You better not pout.\"}, {\"start\": 388.24, \"end\": 389.44, \"text\": \"I'm telling you why.\"}, {\"start\": 389.44, \"end\": 395.08, \"text\": \"Santa Claus is coming to town!\"}, {\"start\": 395.2, \"end\": 397.92, \"text\": \"He sees you when you're sleeping.\"}, {\"start\": 397.92, \"end\": 400.56, \"text\": \"He knows when you're awake.\"}, {\"start\": 400.56, \"end\": 403.8, \"text\": \"He knows if you've been bad or good.\"}, {\"start\": 403.8, \"end\": 407.16, \"text\": \"So be good for goodness sake. Oh...!\"}, {\"start\": 407.16, \"end\": 408.2, \"text\": \"You better watch out.\"}, {\"start\": 408.2, \"end\": 409.52, \"text\": \"You better not cry.\"}, {\"start\": 409.56, \"end\": 410.88, \"text\": \"You better not pout.\"}, {\"start\": 410.96, \"end\": 412.4, \"text\": \"I'm telling you why.\"}, {\"start\": 412.4, \"end\": 417.88, \"text\": \"Santa Claus is coming to town!\"}, {\"start\": 421.56, \"end\": 424.2, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 424.28, \"end\": 425.56, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 425.56, \"end\": 428.2, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 428.28, \"end\": 433.32, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 433.32, \"end\": 441.2, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "Vpb13X1sxdo": {
    "video_id": "Vpb13X1sxdo",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.20.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171121",
    "duration": 473,
    "view_count": 232,
    "description": "November 20, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-GOP SENATORS PUSH FOR TAX REFORM PLAN\n-TRUMP DESIGNATES N. KOREA STATE SPONSOR OF TERRORISM\n-JANET YELLEN SUBMITS RESIGNATION \n-TRIAL FOR SECURITY GUARD ACCUSED OF MURDER\n-GEORGIA DOME IMPLODES\n-CHARLES MANSON DIES AT 83\n-EARLE HYMAN AND DELLA REESE OBITS\n-NATIONAL THANKSGIVING PARDONING CEREMONY\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 11.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.024, \"end\": 14.024, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.025, \"end\": 18.025, \"text\": \"The Senate will debate the tax reform\"}, {\"start\": 18.1, \"end\": 23.1, \"text\": \"reform bill after the Thanksgiving holidays.\"}, {\"start\": 23.1, \"end\": 26.1, \"text\": \"Some senators believe it will pass.\"}, {\"start\": 26.124, \"end\": 29.124, \"text\": \"Others hope it fails.\"}, {\"start\": 30.0, \"end\": 35.0, \"text\": \"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell\"}, {\"start\": 36.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"can only lose two Republican votes.\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 45.0, \"text\": \"And the bill's repeal of the\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 50.0, \"text\": \"individual mandate may prove a step too far\"}, {\"start\": 50.0, \"end\": 55.0, \"text\": \"for some Republicans. That might be why the Trump administration\"}, {\"start\": 55.0, \"end\": 60.0, \"text\": \"is willing to play ball with the bill and negotiate. And while critics say the\"}, {\"start\": 60.0, \"end\": 65.0, \"text\": \"tax reform plan would hurt groups like seniors\"}, {\"start\": 65.0, \"end\": 67.0, \"text\": \"and those with low incomes,\"}, {\"start\": 67.0, \"end\": 73.0, \"text\": \"the White House says it could greatly benefit the middle class.\"}, {\"start\": 74.0, \"end\": 79.0, \"text\": \"President Trump made the announcement during the meeting with his cabinet that he has\"}, {\"start\": 79.0, \"end\": 84.0, \"text\": \"put North Korea back on the list of state sponsors of terrorism.\"}, {\"start\": 85.0, \"end\": 90.0, \"text\": \"The president said it should have happened a long time ago because North\"}, {\"start\": 90.0, \"end\": 95.0, \"text\": \"Korea continues to threaten the world by nuclear devastation and has\"}, {\"start\": 95.0, \"end\": 98.0, \"text\": \"repeatedly supported acts of international terrorism.\"}, {\"start\": 99.0, \"end\": 103.0, \"text\": \"Designating North Korea as a state sponsor of terrorism imposes more\"}, {\"start\": 104.0, \"end\": 108.0, \"text\": \"sanctions including various financial restrictions and limits on economic aid.\"}, {\"start\": 108.0, \"end\": 114.0, \"text\": \"The Treasury Department is expected to give specifics on those sanctions this week.\"}, {\"start\": 117.0, \"end\": 122.0, \"text\": \"Today Federal Reserve chair Janet\"}, {\"start\": 122.0, \"end\": 127.0, \"text\": \"Yellen announced she is resigning from the board. However she says\"}, {\"start\": 127.0, \"end\": 131.0, \"text\": \"she will stay on until her successor, Jerome Powell,\"}, {\"start\": 132.0, \"end\": 135.0, \"text\": \"is sworn in -- which is in February.\"}, {\"start\": 136.0, \"end\": 141.0, \"text\": \"Under the terms of her appointment Yellen had the option to stay and serve as governor\"}, {\"start\": 142.0, \"end\": 146.0, \"text\": \"but chose not to. With her departure that leaves\"}, {\"start\": 147.0, \"end\": 151.0, \"text\": \"four open seats to fill on the Board of Governors.\"}, {\"start\": 151.0, \"end\": 156.0, \"text\": \"President Trump has not yet  nominated anyone to fill those vacancies.\"}, {\"start\": 158.0, \"end\": 163.0, \"text\": \"The trial of Stephen Duxbury resumes this morning\"}, {\"start\": 163.0, \"end\": 168.0, \"text\": \"in Orlando Florida. He's accused of\"}, {\"start\": 168.0, \"end\": 172.0, \"text\": \"killing Sasha Samsudean\"}, {\"start\": 173.0, \"end\": 178.0, \"text\": \"in 2015 at an apartment building where he worked as a security guard.\"}, {\"start\": 178.0, \"end\": 182.0, \"text\": \"On Friday jurors saw pictures from inside\"}, {\"start\": 183.0, \"end\": 187.0, \"text\": \"Samsudean's apartment, including inside the bedroom where she was\"}, {\"start\": 187.0, \"end\": 192.0, \"text\": \"found dead. Prosecutors say Duxbury\"}, {\"start\": 192.0, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"used bleach to destroy evidence.\"}, {\"start\": 196.0, \"end\": 201.0, \"text\": \"Prosecutors are hoping to wrap up their case today.\"}, {\"start\": 204.0, \"end\": 211.0, \"text\": \"After 25 years a spectacular early morning implosion took down the Georgia Dome.\"}, {\"start\": 211.0, \"end\": 219.0, \"text\": \"Take a look. Five, 4, 3, 2,1...\"}, {\"start\": 220.0, \"end\": 224.0, \"text\": \"For the past 25 years the Georgia Dome was home of the NFL's\"}, {\"start\": 225.0, \"end\": 229.0, \"text\": \"Atlanta Falcons but it was also the only facility in the\"}, {\"start\": 229.0, \"end\": 235.0, \"text\": \"world to host the Olympics, Super Bowl and final four.\"}, {\"start\": 235.0, \"end\": 239.0, \"text\": \"It was shut down this year following the opening of nearby\"}, {\"start\": 239.0, \"end\": 243.0, \"text\": \"Mercedes-Benz stadium.\"}, {\"start\": 244.0, \"end\": 248.0, \"text\": \"Plans are underway to replace the dome with a hotel,\"}, {\"start\": 248.0, \"end\": 252.0, \"text\": \"parking and green space.\"}, {\"start\": 253.0, \"end\": 258.0, \"text\": \"Notorious cult leader Charles Manson\"}, {\"start\": 258.0, \"end\": 262.0, \"text\": \"has died. The California Department of Corrections\"}, {\"start\": 262.0, \"end\": 267.0, \"text\": \"says he passed away of natural causes on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 268.0, \"end\": 272.0, \"text\": \"Manson and his followers, a cult known as \\\"The Family\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 273.0, \"end\": 279.0, \"text\": \"were behind a string of gruesome murders in California in 1969.\"}, {\"start\": 279.0, \"end\": 284.0, \"text\": \"The attacks left seven people dead including  pregnant actress\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"Sharon Tate.\"}, {\"start\": 287.824, \"end\": 291.024, \"text\": \"Manson was also convicted in connection with the killing of two others.\"}, {\"start\": 291.025, \"end\": 293.925, \"text\": \"He was serving a total of nine consecutive\"}, {\"start\": 294.0, \"end\": 301.0, \"text\": \"life sentences and was denied parole 12 times.\"}, {\"start\": 301.0, \"end\": 304.0, \"text\": \"Manson was 83 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 306.0, \"end\": 311.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood said goodbye to two legendary actors today.\"}, {\"start\": 311.0, \"end\": 315.0, \"text\": \"Actor and Broadway star\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 321.0, \"text\": \"Earle Hyman died. He's best known for playing\"}, {\"start\": 321.0, \"end\": 326.0, \"text\": \"doctor Heathcliff Huxtable's father, Russell,\"}, {\"start\": 327.0, \"end\": 333.0, \"text\": \"on \\\"The Cosby Show.\\\" His TV granddaughter\"}, {\"start\": 333.0, \"end\": 337.0, \"text\": \"Keisha Knight Pulliam, who played Rudy,\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 343.0, \"text\": \"posted this photo on Instagram saying\"}, {\"start\": 343.0, \"end\": 348.0, \"text\": \"\\\"We have gained another angel.\\\" Hyman died Friday\"}, {\"start\": 348.0, \"end\": 353.0, \"text\": \"at a retirement home in New Jersey. A cause of death was not provided.\"}, {\"start\": 353.0, \"end\": 356.0, \"text\": \"Hyman was 91 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 356.024, \"end\": 359.924, \"text\": \"And Della Reese also died.\"}, {\"start\": 360.0, \"end\": 365.0, \"text\": \"The actress and singer was best known for playing Tess\"}, {\"start\": 366.0, \"end\": 371.0, \"text\": \"on the hit show \\\"Touched By An Angel.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 371.0, \"end\": 375.0, \"text\": \"She also had big roles in the movies \\\"Harlem Nights\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 376.0, \"end\": 382.0, \"text\": \"and \\\"A Thin Line Between Love and Hate.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 382.0, \"end\": 387.0, \"text\": \"Her family says she battled\"}, {\"start\": 387.0, \"end\": 390.0, \"text\": \"diabetes for years. Reese was 86 years old.\"}, {\"start\": 392.0, \"end\": 396.0, \"text\": \"These two turkeys have a lot to be thankful. Their names are\"}, {\"start\": 396.0, \"end\": 401.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Wishbone\\\" and \\\"Drumstick.\\\" Today they were\"}, {\"start\": 401.0, \"end\": 406.0, \"text\": \"both pardoned by President Trump, which means they won't end up on someone's\"}, {\"start\": 406.0, \"end\": 410.0, \"text\": \"Thanksgiving Day dinner table. The turkey pardon tradition started in\"}, {\"start\": 410.0, \"end\": 413.0, \"text\": \"1947 during the Harry Truman\"}, {\"start\": 414.0, \"end\": 419.0, \"text\": \"administration and then it faded away.\"}, {\"start\": 419.0, \"end\": 426.0, \"text\": \"President George H.W. Bush brought it back in 1989.\"}, {\"start\": 426.0, \"end\": 431.0, \"text\": \"As part of the tradition the turkeys stay in the\"}, {\"start\": 431.0, \"end\": 438.0, \"text\": \"Willard Intercontinental Hotel as VIP guests.\"}, {\"start\": 438.0, \"end\": 443.0, \"text\": \"After the pardoning the birds will join last year's turkeys at\"}, {\"start\": 443.0, \"end\": 449.0, \"text\": \"Virginia Tech University to live out the rest of their lives.\"}, {\"start\": 451.0, \"end\": 454.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 454.0, \"end\": 456.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 456.024, \"end\": 460.024, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 460.2, \"end\": 464.2, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-TI-YrX4Zho": {
    "video_id": "-TI-YrX4Zho",
    "title": "Sign1News 6.13.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180614",
    "duration": 562,
    "view_count": 1025,
    "description": "TODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Trump says North Korea no longer a nuclear threat\n-Judge denies P.R. request delay records\n-Western wildfires force thousands to flee\n-Couple shares wedding pics in front of 416 wildfire\n-California to vote on splitting into three states\n-Netflix to continue to streaming Bourdain’s show\n-North America to host 2026 World Cup\n-Orphaned bear cub awaits name and new home",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.34, \"end\": 8.84, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.84, \"end\": 11.02, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.02, \"end\": 12.78, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.78, \"end\": 15.5, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.34, \"end\": 27.54, \"text\": \"President Trump is back in Washington after his history making summit with North Korean\"}, {\"start\": 27.54, \"end\": 38.1, \"text\": \"leader Kim Jong Un and he is assuring Americans that North Korea is no longer a nuclear threat.\"}, {\"start\": 38.1, \"end\": 47.1, \"text\": \"He tweeted this this morning: \\\"Before taking office people were assuming that we were going\"}, {\"start\": 47.1, \"end\": 50.4, \"text\": \"to war with North Korea.\"}, {\"start\": 50.4, \"end\": 58.88, \"text\": \"President Obama said that North Korea was our biggest and most dangerous problem.\"}, {\"start\": 58.96, \"end\": 60.14, \"text\": \"No longer.\"}, {\"start\": 60.14, \"end\": 63.16, \"text\": \"Sleep well tonight!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 63.16, \"end\": 73.62, \"text\": \"But the lack of detail in the joint agreement signed by Trump and Kim is garnering criticism.\"}, {\"start\": 73.62, \"end\": 81.36, \"text\": \"Critics say North Korea still has all of its nuclear weapons and the ability to use them\"}, {\"start\": 81.36, \"end\": 86.62, \"text\": \"and that they have agreed to completely denuclearization multiple times in the past\"}, {\"start\": 86.64, \"end\": 89.12, \"text\": \"but did not follow through.\"}, {\"start\": 89.12, \"end\": 100.4, \"text\": \"Also raising eyebrows is the president's glowing praise for Kim despite his atrocious human\"}, {\"start\": 100.4, \"end\": 105.9, \"text\": \"rights record.\"}, {\"start\": 105.92, \"end\": 109.6, \"text\": \"The president's complimentary comments are in stark contrast to his rhetoric just six\"}, {\"start\": 109.6, \"end\": 112.4, \"text\": \"months ago.\"}, {\"start\": 112.4, \"end\": 116.64, \"text\": \"But Trump insists it was his harsh rhetoric that brought Kim to the negotiating table\"}, {\"start\": 116.64, \"end\": 118.72, \"text\": \"in the first place.\"}, {\"start\": 120.4, \"end\": 128.72, \"text\": \"According to a new court document, the death records from hurricane Maria's devastation\"}, {\"start\": 128.74, \"end\": 131.14, \"text\": \"on Puerto Rico must be released to the press today.\"}, {\"start\": 131.14, \"end\": 138.28, \"text\": \"The Puerto Rican government filed a motion Monday to delay the release of death certificates\"}, {\"start\": 138.28, \"end\": 143.08, \"text\": \"but it was overruled in court.\"}, {\"start\": 143.08, \"end\": 150.88, \"text\": \"Starting Tuesday, the documents will be released to CNN and the Center for Investigative Journalism.\"}, {\"start\": 150.88, \"end\": 158.2, \"text\": \"The two organizations sued for the release of the records in February after evidence\"}, {\"start\": 158.2, \"end\": 161.52, \"text\": \"suggested the death toll was much higher than officials reported.\"}, {\"start\": 161.52, \"end\": 169.12, \"text\": \"The release of the documents will help determine who died, when, how and what caused their death.\"}, {\"start\": 171.2, \"end\": 177.92, \"text\": \"Wildfires in the western US have been causing havoc.\"}, {\"start\": 177.92, \"end\": 183.04, \"text\": \"Some have been burning since late May.\"}, {\"start\": 183.04, \"end\": 191.2, \"text\": \"Thousands of people has been forced to flee as flames scorched tens of thousands of\"}, {\"start\": 191.2, \"end\": 196.64, \"text\": \"acres in several states, including Colorado, California, New Mexico and Washington State.\"}, {\"start\": 196.64, \"end\": 201.44, \"text\": \"Some residents who evacuated were allowed to return home but they been warned they may\"}, {\"start\": 201.44, \"end\": 204.16, \"text\": \"have to leave again.\"}, {\"start\": 204.16, \"end\": 211.52, \"text\": \"Officials closed the San Juan International Forest in Colorado.\"}, {\"start\": 211.52, \"end\": 222.56, \"text\": \"Firefighters say they are using an aggressive air attack to locate and contain the fires.\"}, {\"start\": 227.04, \"end\": 239.2, \"text\": \"A Colorado couple posted their wedding photos taken in front of the 416 wildfire in Colorado.\"}, {\"start\": 239.2, \"end\": 243.84, \"text\": \"They say they did it to show their appreciation for the crews battling the blazes and keeping\"}, {\"start\": 243.84, \"end\": 246.4, \"text\": \"the area safe.\"}, {\"start\": 246.4, \"end\": 253.68, \"text\": \"The photographer says the couple had to move the spot of their wedding because of the fire\"}, {\"start\": 253.68, \"end\": 258.08, \"text\": \"and decided to use the fire for a backdrop.\"}, {\"start\": 258.08, \"end\": 262.96, \"text\": \"The couple says they would like to encourage people to donate to the community foundation\"}, {\"start\": 262.96, \"end\": 266.16, \"text\": \"serving Southwest Colorado.\"}, {\"start\": 266.16, \"end\": 272.0, \"text\": \"There are no reports of any injuries or structures lost however the fire has destroyed more than\"}, {\"start\": 272.0, \"end\": 279.68, \"text\": \"23,000 acres and prompted mandatory evacuations.\"}, {\"start\": 282.32, \"end\": 288.8, \"text\": \"In November Californian's will vote whether to separate into three states: California,\"}, {\"start\": 289.12, \"end\": 296.4, \"text\": \"Northern California and Southern California.\"}, {\"start\": 296.4, \"end\": 306.0, \"text\": \"The proposal is called \\\"Cal 3\\\" and it received over 402,000 valid signatures, which means\"}, {\"start\": 306.0, \"end\": 312.0, \"text\": \"it surpassed the number of signatures required by state law to be on the ballot.\"}, {\"start\": 312.0, \"end\": 319.2, \"text\": \"Supporters of the proposal say splitting California into three states would allow each region\"}, {\"start\": 319.2, \"end\": 324.64, \"text\": \"to address the most pressing issues, including school systems, high taxes, deteriorating\"}, {\"start\": 324.64, \"end\": 331.04, \"text\": \"infrastructure and strained government.\"}, {\"start\": 331.04, \"end\": 339.04, \"text\": \"Critics say \\\"Cal 3\\\" would cost the state billions in tax dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 339.04, \"end\": 344.08, \"text\": \"If the measure is approved by voters, the governor will transfer the notice of state\"}, {\"start\": 344.08, \"end\": 351.44, \"text\": \"approval to Congress, which will then vote to ratify the creation of the new three-state\"}, {\"start\": 351.44, \"end\": 353.28, \"text\": \"structure.\"}, {\"start\": 354.08, \"end\": 367.12, \"text\": \"Famous chef Anthony Bourdain's popular show \\\"Parts Unknown\\\" was set to end its run on\"}, {\"start\": 367.12, \"end\": 371.2, \"text\": \"Netflix this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 371.2, \"end\": 380.4, \"text\": \"But fans mourning Bourdain's death have succeeded in convincing Netflix to continue streaming\"}, {\"start\": 380.4, \"end\": 383.6, \"text\": \"his show.\"}, {\"start\": 383.6, \"end\": 391.44, \"text\": \"One fan started a petition and it attracted more than 6,000 signatures.\"}, {\"start\": 391.44, \"end\": 397.52, \"text\": \"So Netflix sent out a statement saying they are extending its agreement that will keep\"}, {\"start\": 397.52, \"end\": 400.08, \"text\": \"\\\"Parts Unknown\\\" on Netflix for months to come.\"}, {\"start\": 400.48, \"end\": 408.24, \"text\": \"Bourdain took his own life last week in France while working on his series.\"}, {\"start\": 409.6, \"end\": 414.4, \"text\": \"Soccer fans, rejoice!\"}, {\"start\": 414.4, \"end\": 418.32, \"text\": \"The World Cup is coming to the US!\"}, {\"start\": 418.32, \"end\": 426.08, \"text\": \"The International Federation of Association Football (FIFA) has chosen North America to\"}, {\"start\": 426.08, \"end\": 431.02, \"text\": \"host the 2026 World Cup.\"}, {\"start\": 431.04, \"end\": 437.12, \"text\": \"The FIFA World Cup is the world's most widely viewed sporting event.\"}, {\"start\": 437.12, \"end\": 452.32, \"text\": \"The United bid by the US, Canada and Mexico beat a bid from Morocco by a 134-65 vote.\"}, {\"start\": 452.32, \"end\": 459.76, \"text\": \"The last time the US hosted the tournament was in 1994 and Mexico in 1986.\"}, {\"start\": 459.76, \"end\": 463.68, \"text\": \"Canada has never previously hosted.\"}, {\"start\": 463.68, \"end\": 475.12, \"text\": \"The first match of the 2018 tournament begins Thursday with host Russia taking on Saudi Arabia.\"}, {\"start\": 477.28, \"end\": 484.72, \"text\": \"This adorable bear cub needs a name.\"}, {\"start\": 484.72, \"end\": 498.419, \"text\": \"Alaska wildlife troopers found him abandoned after hunters illegally shot and killed his mother.\"}, {\"start\": 498.419, \"end\": 506.88, \"text\": \"Right now the cub is at the zoo in Anchorage, Alaska and has quickly become the star attraction.\"}, {\"start\": 506.88, \"end\": 515.52, \"text\": \"But the tiny, 10 pound baby bear will eventually grow and weigh more than 800 pounds and the\"}, {\"start\": 515.52, \"end\": 520.4, \"text\": \"zoo doesn't have enough room to keep them.\"}, {\"start\": 520.4, \"end\": 528.96, \"text\": \"Once he moves to his new home at Northwest Trek Wildlife Park in Washington State, he\"}, {\"start\": 528.96, \"end\": 531.2, \"text\": \"will be given a name.\"}, {\"start\": 533.28, \"end\": 536.24, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 536.24, \"end\": 537.6, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 537.6, \"end\": 540.48, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 540.48, \"end\": 545.76, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 545.76, \"end\": 548.72, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 548.72, \"end\": 550.08, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 550.08, \"end\": 553.84, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "Ebrdhld-8wM": {
    "video_id": "Ebrdhld-8wM",
    "title": "Dad recreates fireworks show in daughter's bedroom (ASL - 3.22.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180323",
    "duration": 72,
    "view_count": 143,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.16, \"end\": 17.22, \"text\": \"Nevada dad Lyle Coram has re-created Disneyland's iconic fireworks show in his daughter Shelby's\"}, {\"start\": 17.22, \"end\": 18.84, \"text\": \"bedroom.\"}, {\"start\": 21.48, \"end\": 27.0, \"text\": \"Coram works as a stagehand on live shows in Las Vegas.\"}, {\"start\": 27.0, \"end\": 32.08, \"text\": \"His technical expertise came in handy on the bedroom project.\"}, {\"start\": 32.08, \"end\": 43.88, \"text\": \"He used a combination of fiber optics, LED lighting and a projector.\"}, {\"start\": 43.9, \"end\": 48.38, \"text\": \"It took about three months to build.\"}, {\"start\": 48.38, \"end\": 56.28, \"text\": \"He even added features like a \\\"Star Wars\\\" theme.\"}, {\"start\": 56.28, \"end\": 64.02, \"text\": \"Coram says his daughter loves Disneyland and the nightly fireworks show is her favorite part.\"}, {\"start\": 64.08, \"end\": 70.92, \"text\": \"Now she can enjoy them every night.\"}]"
  },
  "82edaN7PsVQ": {
    "video_id": "82edaN7PsVQ",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.9.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171210",
    "duration": 568,
    "view_count": 379,
    "description": "December 9, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-FIRST DEATH REPORTED IN CALIFORNIA WILDFIRES\n-GOVERNMENT SHUTDOWN AVOIDED FOR NOW\n-COPTIC CHURCH EXCUSES ITSELF FROM PENCE MEETING\n-MORE DEMONSTRATIONS OVER U.S. DECISION ON JERUSALEM\n-POLICE FREE MOTORISTS FROM BURNING CAR\n-POLICE RELEASE HILARIOUS GRINCH PSA\n-COUPLE USES STOLEN CREDIT CARD FOR SKYDIVING\n-IT'S SNOWING IN MEXICO!\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.08, \"end\": 9.08, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.14, \"end\": 10.7, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 10.74, \"end\": 13.5, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.4, \"end\": 23.34, \"text\": \"We are sad to report the first death in the California wildfires.\"}, {\"start\": 23.34, \"end\": 31.46, \"text\": \"Officials say a 70-year-old woman was found dead in her car.\"}, {\"start\": 31.54, \"end\": 40.2, \"text\": \"They say she had a traffic accident trying to evacuate and died in a car\"}, {\"start\": 40.22, \"end\": 45.86, \"text\": \"from smoke inhalation and thermal burns.\"}, {\"start\": 45.92, \"end\": 52.44, \"text\": \"Wildfires continue to roar across Southern California for a fifth straight days\"}, {\"start\": 52.44, \"end\": 57.86, \"text\": \"and that has prompted more evacuations.\"}, {\"start\": 57.86, \"end\": 68.58, \"text\": \"Six large wildfires scorched nearly 160,000 acres\"}, {\"start\": 68.62, \"end\": 75.14, \"text\": \"and have forced 190,000 people out of their homes.\"}, {\"start\": 75.2, \"end\": 79.54, \"text\": \"Across the region at least 5,700 firefighters have worked around the clock\"}, {\"start\": 79.56, \"end\": 83.6, \"text\": \"to contain the towering walls of flames.\"}, {\"start\": 83.66, \"end\": 91.02, \"text\": \"Unfortunately, dry conditions and 55 mile-per-hour wind gusts\"}, {\"start\": 91.02, \"end\": 94.56, \"text\": \"continue to make the situation worse, not better.\"}, {\"start\": 96.58, \"end\": 101.18, \"text\": \"The US government avoided a shutdown -- for now.\"}, {\"start\": 101.2, \"end\": 112.6, \"text\": \"The original deadline was Saturday at midnight but Congress approved the funding bill that\"}, {\"start\": 112.6, \"end\": 116.06, \"text\": \"keeps things afloat for a little while longer.\"}, {\"start\": 116.08, \"end\": 124.08, \"text\": \"The House and Senate voted in favor of a measure that keeps federal agencies up and running\"}, {\"start\": 124.09, \"end\": 125.95, \"text\": \"until December 22nd.\"}, {\"start\": 125.95, \"end\": 130.64, \"text\": \"There were 235 \\\"Yeas\\\" and 193 \\\"Nays.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 130.72, \"end\": 138.14, \"text\": \"In order to pass a long-term spending bill Republican and Democratic leaders now have\"}, {\"start\": 138.14, \"end\": 140.96, \"text\": \"to hammer out their differences.\"}, {\"start\": 140.98, \"end\": 153.18, \"text\": \"Over the next two weeks they will debate issues like defense spending and immigration.\"}, {\"start\": 153.18, \"end\": 164.86, \"text\": \"And Democrats say the deferred action for childhood arrivals is a must-have.\"}, {\"start\": 164.86, \"end\": 172.56, \"text\": \"And although there may be some bickering over the next few days behind closed doors,\"}, {\"start\": 172.56, \"end\": 177.56, \"text\": \"there was a sense of optimism as talks began.\"}, {\"start\": 179.98, \"end\": 189.24, \"text\": \"The head of Egypt's Coptic Church will not meet with Vice President Mike Pence when he\"}, {\"start\": 189.24, \"end\": 199.9, \"text\": \"visits the country in mid-December.\"}, {\"start\": 199.92, \"end\": 213.12, \"text\": \"The church issued a statement excusing Coptic Pope Tawadros II from the meeting.\"}, {\"start\": 213.12, \"end\": 216.32, \"text\": \"The reason cited by the statement was the decision to\"}, {\"start\": 216.32, \"end\": 229.12, \"text\": \"recognize Jerusalem as the capital of Israel and move the U.S. Embassy there.\"}, {\"start\": 229.12, \"end\": 231.72, \"text\": \"The statement said Trump's decision was poorly timed\"}, {\"start\": 231.8, \"end\": 236.4, \"text\": \"and didn't consider the feelings of the Arab world.\"}, {\"start\": 238.44, \"end\": 248.43, \"text\": \"Thousands demonstrated peacefully in Beirut Friday against President Trump's decision\"}, {\"start\": 248.44, \"end\": 258.92, \"text\": \"to recognize Jerusalem as Israel's capital.\"}, {\"start\": 259.04, \"end\": 267.44, \"text\": \"Thousands of Lebanese and Palestinians turned out,\"}, {\"start\": 267.56, \"end\": 271.4, \"text\": \"brought together by one of the few issues people in the region can agree upon.\"}, {\"start\": 271.52, \"end\": 282.16, \"text\": \"One young boy said \\\"We should thank Trump because he united the Arabs and the Muslims\"}, {\"start\": 282.2, \"end\": 284.24, \"text\": \"to fight Israel.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 284.24, \"end\": 298.84, \"text\": \"There are more demonstrations planned Sunday outside the U.S. Embassy in Beirut.\"}, {\"start\": 301.12, \"end\": 311.04, \"text\": \"This body cam video shows the desperate determination of Atlanta police trying to save two people\"}, {\"start\": 311.08, \"end\": 318.56, \"text\": \"trapped in a burning car.\"}, {\"start\": 318.64, \"end\": 321.92, \"text\": \"The doors of the car are jammed.\"}, {\"start\": 322.0, \"end\": 326.84, \"text\": \"A fire extinguisher fails to douse the fire.\"}, {\"start\": 326.84, \"end\": 334.56, \"text\": \"And officer's batons are just bouncing off the windows.\"}, {\"start\": 334.72, \"end\": 338.4, \"text\": \"The people inside are screaming -- knowing they are minutes away from a horrible death\"}, {\"start\": 338.419, \"end\": 340.74, \"text\": \"if they don't get out.\"}, {\"start\": 340.74, \"end\": 345.92, \"text\": \"The fire department is on the way but time is running out.\"}, {\"start\": 346.04, \"end\": 356.32, \"text\": \"The police have no equipment to pry the doors open so they try to keep the flames under\"}, {\"start\": 356.32, \"end\": 363.28, \"text\": \"control by pouring water from a jug on the burning car.\"}, {\"start\": 363.28, \"end\": 370.16, \"text\": \"Firefighters finally arrived, put out the flames and free the passengers -- who survive.\"}, {\"start\": 372.0, \"end\": 382.2, \"text\": \"Police in Tucson, Arizona released this Dr. Seuss-inspired video to encourage residents\"}, {\"start\": 382.2, \"end\": 388.92, \"text\": \"to protect their belongings this holiday season.\"}, {\"start\": 388.92, \"end\": 401.92, \"text\": \"It's entitled \\\"Don't Let a Grinch Ruin Your Holidays This Year.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 402.04, \"end\": 416.16, \"text\": \"It stars a slinking grinch-like character rifling through belongings and parked cars\"}, {\"start\": 416.16, \"end\": 420.4, \"text\": \"before the cops arrive to take him away.\"}, {\"start\": 420.44, \"end\": 429.96, \"text\": \"Police are hoping the video will encourage locals to lock their cars when shopping.\"}, {\"start\": 429.96, \"end\": 438.04, \"text\": \"The video has been viewed more than 80,000 times.\"}, {\"start\": 441.64, \"end\": 451.92, \"text\": \"Suffolk County police are offering a $5,000 reward for information that would lead to\"}, {\"start\": 452.04, \"end\": 457.28, \"text\": \"the arrest of these two people.\"}, {\"start\": 457.36, \"end\": 469.12, \"text\": \"Police say this couple used a stolen credit card to pay for two skydives in Long Island,\"}, {\"start\": 469.12, \"end\": 475.28, \"text\": \"New York in June.\"}, {\"start\": 475.32, \"end\": 478.52, \"text\": \"They also paid the skydive center to take this video\"}, {\"start\": 478.52, \"end\": 483.44, \"text\": \"that investigators later got hold of.\"}, {\"start\": 483.56, \"end\": 492.0, \"text\": \"Police are asking anyone who may recognize the couple to contact the Suffolk County crimestoppers.\"}, {\"start\": 493.84, \"end\": 506.44, \"text\": \"Parts of Texas and the southern states experienced some rare snowfall.\"}, {\"start\": 506.44, \"end\": 509.999, \"text\": \"And it's also snowing south of the border.\"}, {\"start\": 510.0, \"end\": 522.44, \"text\": \"These pictures are from Gomez Palazio in Mexico's Durango state.\"}, {\"start\": 522.48, \"end\": 527.52, \"text\": \"The first winter storm of the season began in the northern part of Mexico.\"}, {\"start\": 527.72, \"end\": 533.08, \"text\": \"It's expected to move to the northeastern United States this weekend with 6 to 8 inches\"}, {\"start\": 533.08, \"end\": 538.8, \"text\": \"of snow predicted for Boston.\"}, {\"start\": 540.96, \"end\": 543.28, \"text\": \"And those your top stories today.\"}, {\"start\": 543.36, \"end\": 545.04, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 545.28, \"end\": 547.44, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 547.6, \"end\": 553.68, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 553.76, \"end\": 561.28, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "4NMULDVMXXA": {
    "video_id": "4NMULDVMXXA",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.27.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171028",
    "duration": 521,
    "view_count": 268,
    "description": "October 27, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-TIGER WOODS PLEADS GUILTY TO RECKLESS DRIVING\n-HARVEY WEINSTEIN SUES THE WEINSTEIN COMPANY\n-ROSE MCGOWAN SPEAKS  \n-73K PEOPLE FLED TO FLORIDA AFTER HURRICANE MARIA  \n-BREAST CANCER MYTHS  \n-PRE-ORDERS FOR IPHONE X SELL OUT IN MINUTES \n-WALMART WILL HAVE ROBOTS ROAMING THE AISLES\n-HOSPITAL DRESSES PREEMIES FOR HALLOWEEN\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.0, \"end\": 21.0, \"text\": \"Today in Florida Tiger\"}, {\"start\": 22.0, \"end\": 27.0, \"text\": \"Woods was in court and pled guilty to reckless driving.\"}, {\"start\": 27.0, \"end\": 32.0, \"text\": \"Back in May a police officer found\"}, {\"start\": 32.0, \"end\": 37.0, \"text\": \"Woods unconscious behind the wheel of his parked car.\"}, {\"start\": 37.0, \"end\": 42.0, \"text\": \"He was arrested for driving under the influence. He had\"}, {\"start\": 43.0, \"end\": 47.0, \"text\": \"no alcohol in his system.\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 52.0, \"text\": \"But a toxicology report showed that\"}, {\"start\": 52.0, \"end\": 56.0, \"text\": \"he did have pain,\"}, {\"start\": 57.0, \"end\": 62.0, \"text\": \"anxiety and sleeping medications plus marijuana in his system at\"}, {\"start\": 62.0, \"end\": 64.0, \"text\": \"the time of his arrest.\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 69.0, \"text\": \"Woods will not serve jail time. Instead he\"}, {\"start\": 69.0, \"end\": 73.0, \"text\": \"agreed to a plea deal that includes 12 months probation and\"}, {\"start\": 74.0, \"end\": 78.0, \"text\": \"50 hours of community service. He will also pay a fine,\"}, {\"start\": 79.0, \"end\": 84.0, \"text\": \"court fees and complete DUI school.\"}, {\"start\": 87.0, \"end\": 91.0, \"text\": \"Harvey Weinstein is\"}, {\"start\": 91.0, \"end\": 96.0, \"text\": \"suing the company that he co-founded. Weinstein\"}, {\"start\": 96.0, \"end\": 101.0, \"text\": \"is the former movie producer who has been accused of dozens of\"}, {\"start\": 101.0, \"end\": 105.0, \"text\": \"incidents of sexual harassment and rape. He is suing the\"}, {\"start\": 105.0, \"end\": 110.0, \"text\": \"Weinstein Company to gain access\"}, {\"start\": 111.0, \"end\": 115.0, \"text\": \"to personnel and employment records\"}, {\"start\": 115.0, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"from the film studio. The lawsuit claims if Weinstein can\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 125.0, \"text\": \"examine that information he can more efficiently assist the\"}, {\"start\": 125.0, \"end\": 130.0, \"text\": \"company in defending against sexual harassment and rape claims.\"}, {\"start\": 130.0, \"end\": 135.0, \"text\": \"When Weinstein's lawyer previously made his demands\"}, {\"start\": 136.0, \"end\": 140.0, \"text\": \"the Weinstein company denied access to all\"}, {\"start\": 140.0, \"end\": 147.0, \"text\": \"information except the code of conduct.\"}, {\"start\": 150.0, \"end\": 154.0, \"text\": \"Actress Rose McGowan has made her\"}, {\"start\": 154.0, \"end\": 157.0, \"text\": \"first public appearance since\"}, {\"start\": 158.0, \"end\": 162.0, \"text\": \"posting on Twitter that Harvey\"}, {\"start\": 163.0, \"end\": 167.0, \"text\": \"Weinstein raped her. She spoke at a\"}, {\"start\": 167.0, \"end\": 172.0, \"text\": \"women's convention in Detroit. She said she was\"}, {\"start\": 172.0, \"end\": 177.0, \"text\": \"silent for 20 years about being sexually harassed and\"}, {\"start\": 177.0, \"end\": 182.0, \"text\": \"she refuses to be silent any more. She said\"}, {\"start\": 182.0, \"end\": 187.0, \"text\": \"it's time for all women to be brave\"}, {\"start\": 187.0, \"end\": 189.0, \"text\": \"and speak up as well.\"}, {\"start\": 192.0, \"end\": 196.0, \"text\": \"According to Florida Governor Rick Scott\"}, {\"start\": 196.0, \"end\": 201.0, \"text\": \"more than seventy three thousand people have arrived in Florida since\"}, {\"start\": 201.0, \"end\": 205.0, \"text\": \"October 3rd. State officials are doing what they can to\"}, {\"start\": 205.0, \"end\": 210.0, \"text\": \"provide aid to the hurricane victims\"}, {\"start\": 210.0, \"end\": 214.0, \"text\": \"who are relocating to Florida and to those who decided\"}, {\"start\": 214.0, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"to stay in Puerto Rico.\"}, {\"start\": 217.0, \"end\": 221.0, \"text\": \"Florida schools have begun enrolling displaced students\"}, {\"start\": 221.0, \"end\": 226.0, \"text\": \"and some Florida colleges and university are waiving\"}, {\"start\": 226.0, \"end\": 229.0, \"text\": \"out-of-state tuition fees.\"}, {\"start\": 233.0, \"end\": 236.0, \"text\": \"October is Breast Cancer\"}, {\"start\": 237.0, \"end\": 241.0, \"text\": \"Awareness Month. According to the American Cancer Society\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 245.0, \"text\": \"breast cancer is the most common cancer in American women.\"}, {\"start\": 245.0, \"end\": 251.0, \"text\": \"It is the second leading cause of cancer deaths in women.\"}, {\"start\": 251.0, \"end\": 256.0, \"text\": \"An estimated 250,000 new cases of breast cancer\"}, {\"start\": 256.0, \"end\": 261.0, \"text\": \"will be diagnosed in 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 261.0, \"end\": 264.0, \"text\": \"Doctors strongly recommend\"}, {\"start\": 265.0, \"end\": 270.0, \"text\": \"monthly self-examinations and yearly mammograms.\"}, {\"start\": 271.0, \"end\": 274.0, \"text\": \"But there are a lot of myths about the\"}, {\"start\": 274.0, \"end\": 280.0, \"text\": \"disease that doctors want to clear up.\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 285.0, \"text\": \"Just because you don't have a family history of breast cancer\"}, {\"start\": 285.0, \"end\": 291.0, \"text\": \"doesn't mean you can't get breast cancer.\"}, {\"start\": 291.0, \"end\": 297.0, \"text\": \"Breast cancer doesn't just affect women.\"}, {\"start\": 297.0, \"end\": 302.0, \"text\": \"Men get breast cancer too. About two thousand men\"}, {\"start\": 302.0, \"end\": 306.0, \"text\": \"will be diagnosed with breast cancer this year.\"}, {\"start\": 307.0, \"end\": 314.0, \"text\": \"Anti-perspirants and deodorants do not cause breast cancer.\"}, {\"start\": 314.0, \"end\": 318.0, \"text\": \"Drinking caffeine does not\"}, {\"start\": 318.0, \"end\": 326.0, \"text\": \"increase your chance of getting breast cancer.\"}, {\"start\": 326.0, \"end\": 330.0, \"text\": \"And wearing an underwire bra does not\"}, {\"start\": 330.0, \"end\": 336.0, \"text\": \"cause breast cancer.\"}, {\"start\": 339.0, \"end\": 344.0, \"text\": \"Good luck getting your hands on the new iPhone10.\"}, {\"start\": 345.0, \"end\": 352.0, \"text\": \"Pre-orders for the smartphone opened at 12:01am\"}, {\"start\": 352.0, \"end\": 355.0, \"text\": \"Pacific Time on Friday,\"}, {\"start\": 355.0, \"end\": 360.0, \"text\": \"a week ahead of the November 3rd launch.\"}, {\"start\": 360.0, \"end\": 364.0, \"text\": \"But the initial supply sold out in\"}, {\"start\": 364.0, \"end\": 369.0, \"text\": \"just a few minutes. That\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 373.0, \"text\": \"means most people won't be able to get the iPhone 10 until\"}, {\"start\": 373.0, \"end\": 378.0, \"text\": \"after November 3rd. They'll have to wait five to six weeks\"}, {\"start\": 378.0, \"end\": 383.0, \"text\": \"for the next shipment.\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 387.0, \"text\": \"The starting price for the new phone\"}, {\"start\": 387.024, \"end\": 389.024, \"text\": \"is $999.\"}, {\"start\": 392.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"Wal-Mart is testing robots in a couple of stores in Arkansas and California.\"}, {\"start\": 398.0, \"end\": 404.0, \"text\": \"They will be used to scan for out of stock\"}, {\"start\": 404.0, \"end\": 409.0, \"text\": \"items, incorrect prices\"}, {\"start\": 409.0, \"end\": 414.0, \"text\": \"and missing labels.\"}, {\"start\": 414.0, \"end\": 418.0, \"text\": \"Wal-Mart officials say the robots\"}, {\"start\": 418.0, \"end\": 425.0, \"text\": \"are more efficient and quicker than\"}, {\"start\": 425.0, \"end\": 429.0, \"text\": \"human employees. The company hopes\"}, {\"start\": 430.0, \"end\": 432.0, \"text\": \"to have robots in at least 50\"}, {\"start\": 432.0, \"end\": 438.0, \"text\": \"stores by the end of January 2018.\"}, {\"start\": 440.0, \"end\": 444.0, \"text\": \"Halloween is next week. Boston Hospital\"}, {\"start\": 444.0, \"end\": 448.0, \"text\": \"wanted to make sure its tiniest superheroes\"}, {\"start\": 448.0, \"end\": 453.0, \"text\": \"are dressed for the occasion.\"}, {\"start\": 453.0, \"end\": 460.0, \"text\": \"The nonprofit project Sweet Peas\"}, {\"start\": 460.0, \"end\": 465.0, \"text\": \"teamed up with the hospital to turn the preemies into the\"}, {\"start\": 465.0, \"end\": 470.0, \"text\": \"cutest characters you have ever seen.\"}, {\"start\": 470.0, \"end\": 476.0, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 476.024, \"end\": 478.024, \"text\": \"The costumes were handmade by\"}, {\"start\": 479.0, \"end\": 485.0, \"text\": \"volunteers and parents of\"}, {\"start\": 485.0, \"end\": 493.0, \"text\": \"former preemies. The hospital even hosted a photo shoot.\"}, {\"start\": 496.0, \"end\": 499.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 499.0, \"end\": 503.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Remember to like us on Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 503.0, \"end\": 505.0, \"text\": \"and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 505.024, \"end\": 512.024, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "zLrTP3whdb0": {
    "video_id": "zLrTP3whdb0",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.8.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180108",
    "duration": 636,
    "view_count": 1881,
    "description": "1.8.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Oprah Winfrey considers running for president\n-Golden Globes dominated by women-centered projects\n-College Football National Championship game\n-Trump allies defend his mental fitness \n-2017 costliest year for natural disasters\n-Apple investors fight Iphone addiction in kids\n-Pink to sing National Anthem at Super Bowl 52\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.78, \"end\": 6.44, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.44, \"end\": 7.98, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 7.98, \"end\": 9.08, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 9.08, \"end\": 11.42, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 13.98, \"end\": 24.32, \"text\": \"Two of Oprah Winfrey's closest friends say she is actively thinking about running for\"}, {\"start\": 24.32, \"end\": 26.48, \"text\": \"president.\"}, {\"start\": 26.48, \"end\": 34.56, \"text\": \"The term \\\"President Winfrey\\\" started floating around last night after she accepted the\"}, {\"start\": 34.56, \"end\": 40.14, \"text\": \"Cecil B. DeMille award at the Golden Globes last night.\"}, {\"start\": 40.14, \"end\": 51.86, \"text\": \"Her rousing acceptance speech spurred chatter about a 2020 presidential run and some of\"}, {\"start\": 51.86, \"end\": 54.96, \"text\": \"Winfrey's closest confidants have been privately urging her to run.\"}, {\"start\": 54.96, \"end\": 63.6, \"text\": \"Even her long time partner Stedman Graham said a presidential run is a possibility.\"}, {\"start\": 63.7, \"end\": 79.84, \"text\": \"Some political strategists say her fame, wealth and popularity could make her a good candidate.\"}, {\"start\": 79.86, \"end\": 88.7, \"text\": \"But others say she lacks political experience and they doubt Americans would choose a TV\"}, {\"start\": 88.7, \"end\": 96.32, \"text\": \"star as president twice in a row.\"}, {\"start\": 96.32, \"end\": 102.8, \"text\": \"A representative for Winfrey did not respond to a request for comment.\"}, {\"start\": 105.06, \"end\": 115.64, \"text\": \"Last night's Golden Globes awards were dominated by movies and TV series centered on women.\"}, {\"start\": 115.64, \"end\": 127.3, \"text\": \"\\\"Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri\\\" was the most honored movie, winning four trophies,\"}, {\"start\": 127.38, \"end\": 128.74, \"text\": \"including best motion picture drama.\"}, {\"start\": 128.74, \"end\": 138.08, \"text\": \"The movie is about a young woman's rape and murder and her mother's pursuit of justice.\"}, {\"start\": 138.08, \"end\": 144.16, \"text\": \"The top TV winner was \\\"Big Little Lies.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 144.3, \"end\": 149.9, \"text\": \"It won four Golden Globes and its storylines involve sexual abuse.\"}, {\"start\": 149.96, \"end\": 159.68, \"text\": \"In fact, all of the night's multiple award winners were stories about women: \\\"Lady Bird\\\",\"}, {\"start\": 159.68, \"end\": 173.04, \"text\": \"\\\"The Shape of Water\\\", \\\"The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel\\\" and \\\"The Handmaid's Tale.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 173.04, \"end\": 185.66, \"text\": \"And Oprah Winfrey became the first black woman ever to receive the Globes's Cecil B. DeMille\"}, {\"start\": 185.66, \"end\": 190.68, \"text\": \"award.\"}, {\"start\": 190.68, \"end\": 202.74, \"text\": \"She brought the audience to its feet with her speech.\"}, {\"start\": 202.74, \"end\": 212.7, \"text\": \"She said she wants all the girls watching to know that a new day is on the horizon and\"}, {\"start\": 212.7, \"end\": 223.56, \"text\": \"it will be because a lot of magnificent women are fighting hard now to make sure those little\"}, {\"start\": 223.56, \"end\": 232.18, \"text\": \"girls become leaders who never have to say \\\"Me Too\\\" again.\"}, {\"start\": 235.12, \"end\": 242.26, \"text\": \"Thousands of college football fans have converged in Atlanta for tonight's big national championship\"}, {\"start\": 242.26, \"end\": 243.62, \"text\": \"game.\"}, {\"start\": 243.62, \"end\": 253.82, \"text\": \"The Georgia Bulldogs will take on the Alabama Crimson Tide in the $1.5 billion Mercedes-Benz\"}, {\"start\": 253.82, \"end\": 258.02, \"text\": \"Stadium.\"}, {\"start\": 258.02, \"end\": 259.96, \"text\": \"Game time is at 8 PM.\"}, {\"start\": 259.96, \"end\": 263.9, \"text\": \"President Trump will be at the game.\"}, {\"start\": 263.9, \"end\": 269.34, \"text\": \"He left Washington D.C. early this morning to make a stop in Tennessee before heading\"}, {\"start\": 269.34, \"end\": 271.68, \"text\": \"to Georgia.\"}, {\"start\": 271.68, \"end\": 282.28, \"text\": \"Trump is expected to be joined at the game by Agriculture Secretary and former Georgia\"}, {\"start\": 282.3, \"end\": 293.02, \"text\": \"Governor Sonny Perdue and Nick Ayers, a Georgia native and Chief of Staff to Vice President\"}, {\"start\": 293.02, \"end\": 295.9, \"text\": \"Mike Pence.\"}, {\"start\": 295.9, \"end\": 300.48, \"text\": \"And big congratulations to this young lady.\"}, {\"start\": 300.48, \"end\": 308.28, \"text\": \"12-year-old Carly Ortega will sign the national anthem.\"}, {\"start\": 308.28, \"end\": 317.06, \"text\": \"She attends Atlanta Area School for the Deaf and will be signing in honor of her mother\"}, {\"start\": 317.16, \"end\": 322.72, \"text\": \"who passed away recently after a long battle with cancer.\"}, {\"start\": 322.72, \"end\": 326.86, \"text\": \"Her mother was a huge Georgia Bulldog fan.\"}, {\"start\": 326.86, \"end\": 329.12, \"text\": \"We are proud of you Carly!\"}, {\"start\": 331.96, \"end\": 338.14, \"text\": \"Members of President Trump's administration are coming to his defense.\"}, {\"start\": 338.14, \"end\": 344.48, \"text\": \"They insist Trump is fit to serve despite questions about his mental stability raised\"}, {\"start\": 344.48, \"end\": 347.74, \"text\": \"in the new tell-all book \\\"Fire and Fury.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 347.74, \"end\": 353.88, \"text\": \"The President himself sent a flurry of tweets in his own defense.\"}, {\"start\": 353.9, \"end\": 360.68, \"text\": \"He said \\\"throughout my life, my two greatest assets have been mental stability and being,\"}, {\"start\": 360.68, \"end\": 362.72, \"text\": \"like, really smart.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 362.72, \"end\": 370.22, \"text\": \"He tweeted that he is a \\\"very stable genius.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 370.22, \"end\": 381.06, \"text\": \"But the author of \\\"Fire and Fury\\\" Michael Wolff is standing by his book.\"}, {\"start\": 381.06, \"end\": 389.8, \"text\": \"He said the president's mental fitness is regularly discussed by Trump's aides, along\"}, {\"start\": 389.8, \"end\": 402.06, \"text\": \"with the 25th amendment, which spells out steps that should be taken in the event the\"}, {\"start\": 402.06, \"end\": 404.86, \"text\": \"president is removed from office.\"}, {\"start\": 408.22, \"end\": 419.42, \"text\": \"According to the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) 2017 was the most expensive\"}, {\"start\": 419.42, \"end\": 424.1, \"text\": \"year on record due to natural disasters.\"}, {\"start\": 424.1, \"end\": 431.04, \"text\": \"Hurricanes Harvey, Irma and Maria, the California wildfires and other natural disasters cost\"}, {\"start\": 431.04, \"end\": 444.32, \"text\": \"$306 billion in total damages.\"}, {\"start\": 444.32, \"end\": 453.62, \"text\": \"Hurricane Harvey was the year's most expensive disaster, causing $125 billion in damages\"}, {\"start\": 453.62, \"end\": 456.04, \"text\": \"by itself.\"}, {\"start\": 456.16, \"end\": 462.06, \"text\": \"The storms combined caused 251 deaths.\"}, {\"start\": 462.06, \"end\": 474.6, \"text\": \"The West Coast wildfires caused $18 billion and caused 54 deaths.\"}, {\"start\": 474.6, \"end\": 483.36, \"text\": \"Other costs came from tornadoes, droughts and flooding.\"}, {\"start\": 485.88, \"end\": 493.9, \"text\": \"Two of Apple's top investors are calling on the company to do more to fight iPhone addiction\"}, {\"start\": 493.9, \"end\": 497.56, \"text\": \"among children and teens.\"}, {\"start\": 497.56, \"end\": 507.4, \"text\": \"The California state teacher's retirement system and JANA partners own about $2 billion\"}, {\"start\": 507.52, \"end\": 510.14, \"text\": \"in Apple stock.\"}, {\"start\": 510.14, \"end\": 519.82, \"text\": \"In a letter posted online to Apple, the shareholders noted studies regarding the detrimental effects\"}, {\"start\": 519.82, \"end\": 525.52, \"text\": \"of smart phone addiction.\"}, {\"start\": 525.52, \"end\": 536.28, \"text\": \"Those issues include lack of sleep and a high risk of depression and suicide.\"}, {\"start\": 536.28, \"end\": 546.06, \"text\": \"The shareholders say Apple should set a better example for its youngest users.\"}, {\"start\": 546.06, \"end\": 554.5, \"text\": \"They encouraged Apple to develop more sophisticated parental controls for its devices to limit\"}, {\"start\": 554.5, \"end\": 557.4, \"text\": \"children's time on them.\"}, {\"start\": 557.4, \"end\": 562.66, \"text\": \"Apple has yet to comment on the letter.\"}, {\"start\": 565.94, \"end\": 581.66, \"text\": \"Today the NFL and NBC announced multiple Grammy award-winning artist Pink will perform the\"}, {\"start\": 581.66, \"end\": 584.18, \"text\": \"national anthem for Super Bowl LII next month.\"}, {\"start\": 584.18, \"end\": 590.66, \"text\": \"This will be the first time Pink has performed at a Super Bowl.\"}, {\"start\": 590.7, \"end\": 596.32, \"text\": \"The game is on February 4th in Minneapolis.\"}, {\"start\": 596.38, \"end\": 602.1, \"text\": \"Then she'll have less than a month to rest.\"}, {\"start\": 602.12, \"end\": 612.6, \"text\": \"Her \\\"Beautiful Trauma\\\" world tour begins March 1st.\"}, {\"start\": 614.86, \"end\": 617.12, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 617.18, \"end\": 618.36, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 618.36, \"end\": 620.5, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 620.5, \"end\": 624.62, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 624.64, \"end\": 629.84, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "SI19V4-BXIs": {
    "video_id": "SI19V4-BXIs",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.28.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171029",
    "duration": 503,
    "view_count": 224,
    "description": "October 28, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-FIRST CHARGES FILED IN MUELLER INVESTIGATION\n-U.S. SERVICE MEMBER DIES IN HELICOPTER CRASH\n-MORE WOMEN SAY BUSH SR TOUCHED THEM INAPPROPRIATELY  \n-OBAMA CALLED FOR JURY DUTY  \n-TOURISTS STILL GOING TO LAS VEGAS DESPITE SHOOTING  \n-MYSTERY OBJECT FROM OUTSIDE OUR SOLAR SYSTEM? \n-TODAY IS NATIONAL CHOCOLATE DAY\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to del",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am at Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.0, \"end\": 23.0, \"text\": \"In May special counsel\"}, {\"start\": 24.0, \"end\": 29.0, \"text\": \"Robert Mueller was\"}, {\"start\": 29.0, \"end\": 34.0, \"text\": \"appointed to lead the investigation\"}, {\"start\": 34.0, \"end\": 39.0, \"text\": \"into Russian meddling in the 2016 presidential\"}, {\"start\": 39.0, \"end\": 43.0, \"text\": \"election. The investigation focused\"}, {\"start\": 43.0, \"end\": 48.0, \"text\": \"on potential collusion between the Trump campaign\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"and Russia, as well as obstruction of justice by the president -- who might have\"}, {\"start\": 53.0, \"end\": 58.0, \"text\": \"tried to impede the investigation. Today in Washington D.C.\"}, {\"start\": 58.0, \"end\": 63.0, \"text\": \"a federal grand jury approved the first charges in that investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 63.0, \"end\": 68.0, \"text\": \"Even though the charges were sealed\"}, {\"start\": 69.0, \"end\": 74.0, \"text\": \"sources close to the investigation say anyone charged in the case could be\"}, {\"start\": 74.0, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"taken into custody as early as Monday.\"}, {\"start\": 81.0, \"end\": 86.0, \"text\": \"It is unclear what the specific charges are.\"}, {\"start\": 86.0, \"end\": 89.0, \"text\": \"In addition to Muller's investigation,\"}, {\"start\": 91.0, \"end\": 96.0, \"text\": \"three committees on Capitol Hill\"}, {\"start\": 97.0, \"end\": 101.0, \"text\": \"are conducting its own investigations.\"}, {\"start\": 105.0, \"end\": 111.0, \"text\": \"In Afghanistan\"}, {\"start\": 111.0, \"end\": 117.0, \"text\": \"an investigation is under way in a deadly U.S. helicopter crash.\"}, {\"start\": 117.0, \"end\": 122.0, \"text\": \"Military officials say the chopper went down Friday night\"}, {\"start\": 122.0, \"end\": 128.0, \"text\": \"in the Logar province\"}, {\"start\": 128.0, \"end\": 133.0, \"text\": \"killing one American crew member.\"}, {\"start\": 133.0, \"end\": 137.0, \"text\": \"Six other U.S. service members were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 143.0, \"text\": \"Investigators have secured the crash site and say the crash\"}, {\"start\": 143.0, \"end\": 147.0, \"text\": \"was not a result of enemy action.\"}, {\"start\": 152.0, \"end\": 156.0, \"text\": \"More women have come forward\"}, {\"start\": 156.0, \"end\": 160.0, \"text\": \"and accused former President George\"}, {\"start\": 161.0, \"end\": 165.0, \"text\": \"H.W. Bush of touching them inappropriately.\"}, {\"start\": 165.0, \"end\": 170.0, \"text\": \"The accusers are actress Jordana\"}, {\"start\": 171.0, \"end\": 177.0, \"text\": \"Grolnick, actress Heather\"}, {\"start\": 177.0, \"end\": 182.0, \"text\": \"Lind and a\"}, {\"start\": 182.0, \"end\": 187.0, \"text\": \"third woman who wishes to remain anonymous. The three women described\"}, {\"start\": 187.0, \"end\": 191.0, \"text\": \"similar stories about how Bush Sr.\"}, {\"start\": 191.0, \"end\": 197.0, \"text\": \"told a sexually explicit joke and then touched them.\"}, {\"start\": 197.0, \"end\": 202.0, \"text\": \"A spokesperson for Bush acknowledged\"}, {\"start\": 202.0, \"end\": 206.0, \"text\": \"the incidents did happen but\"}, {\"start\": 207.0, \"end\": 212.0, \"text\": \"he said the jokes and actions were intended to be good natured\"}, {\"start\": 213.0, \"end\": 220.0, \"text\": \"but apologized to anyone who was offended.\"}, {\"start\": 223.0, \"end\": 227.0, \"text\": \"Former President Obama has\"}, {\"start\": 227.0, \"end\": 234.0, \"text\": \"been summonded for jury duty in Illinois.\"}, {\"start\": 234.0, \"end\": 241.0, \"text\": \"The former president lives in Washington D.C. but he maintains a home in Chicago.\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 245.0, \"text\": \"The jury summon says Obama needs to report to jury duty next month.\"}, {\"start\": 246.0, \"end\": 250.0, \"text\": \"Obama says he plans to show up.\"}, {\"start\": 251.0, \"end\": 256.0, \"text\": \"He is not the first former president to receive a jury summons.\"}, {\"start\": 256.0, \"end\": 259.0, \"text\": \"Two years ago in Dallas\"}, {\"start\": 260.0, \"end\": 265.0, \"text\": \"President George W. Bush\"}, {\"start\": 265.0, \"end\": 269.0, \"text\": \"reported for jury duty\"}, {\"start\": 269.0, \"end\": 272.0, \"text\": \"but he was not selected.\"}, {\"start\": 276.024, \"end\": 278.999, \"text\": \"Earlier this month a shooting in Las Vegas\"}, {\"start\": 279.0, \"end\": 283.0, \"text\": \"killed 58 people and wounded nearly 500.\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 292.0, \"text\": \"But that tragedy doesn't seem to be affecting tourism.\"}, {\"start\": 292.0, \"end\": 296.0, \"text\": \"Several casinos in the area say they have not\"}, {\"start\": 296.0, \"end\": 301.0, \"text\": \"seen a significant drop in guests.\"}, {\"start\": 302.0, \"end\": 307.0, \"text\": \"In fact profits at some casinos increased.\"}, {\"start\": 307.0, \"end\": 311.0, \"text\": \"However we will know soon if profits dropped at MGM.\"}, {\"start\": 311.0, \"end\": 316.0, \"text\": \"MGM owns Mandalay Bay which is where\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 318.0, \"text\": \"the shooting took place.\"}, {\"start\": 318.0, \"end\": 326.0, \"text\": \"Those numbers will be released next month.\"}, {\"start\": 329.0, \"end\": 332.0, \"text\": \"NASA scientists are\"}, {\"start\": 333.0, \"end\": 338.0, \"text\": \"pointing their telescopes at the sky. They\"}, {\"start\": 338.0, \"end\": 342.0, \"text\": \"are trying to identify a mystery object that keeps\"}, {\"start\": 342.0, \"end\": 347.0, \"text\": \"showing up. Experts think it is less than\"}, {\"start\": 347.0, \"end\": 352.0, \"text\": \"a quarter of a mile in diameter and is traveling at\"}, {\"start\": 352.0, \"end\": 356.0, \"text\": \"more than 15 miles per second.\"}, {\"start\": 357.0, \"end\": 362.0, \"text\": \"Last Friday this mystery rock was first seen by a\"}, {\"start\": 362.0, \"end\": 368.0, \"text\": \"university researcher in Hawaii.\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 374.0, \"text\": \"And scientists think it passed by Earth five days before that.\"}, {\"start\": 375.0, \"end\": 380.0, \"text\": \"The strange behavior of this object doesn't\"}, {\"start\": 381.0, \"end\": 385.0, \"text\": \"match any typical orbit they have seen and\"}, {\"start\": 386.0, \"end\": 391.0, \"text\": \"that makes NASA think the object is\"}, {\"start\": 391.024, \"end\": 398.024, \"text\": \"from outside our solar system.\"}, {\"start\": 399.0, \"end\": 404.0, \"text\": \"Once researchers determine what the object is\"}, {\"start\": 404.024, \"end\": 410.024, \"text\": \"it may get a proper name. For now is just being called A-20-17-U-1.\"}, {\"start\": 413.0, \"end\": 418.0, \"text\": \"Today October 28th is National Chocolate Day.\"}, {\"start\": 418.0, \"end\": 422.0, \"text\": \"National Chocolate Day was created by the\"}, {\"start\": 422.0, \"end\": 429.0, \"text\": \"National Confectioners Association.\"}, {\"start\": 430.001, \"end\": 435.001, \"text\": \"Chocolate is America's favorite flavor.\"}, {\"start\": 438.1, \"end\": 443.1, \"text\": \"dark chocolate, white chocolate, milk chocolate.\"}, {\"start\": 443.101, \"end\": 446.901, \"text\": \"Some people have gone so far as to make\"}, {\"start\": 447.0, \"end\": 452.0, \"text\": \"chocolate lasagna and chocolate covered bacon.\"}, {\"start\": 452.0, \"end\": 457.0, \"text\": \"There are some health benefits to eating chocolate. Doctors say\"}, {\"start\": 458.0, \"end\": 463.0, \"text\": \"if you eat it in moderation, it can lower your blood pressure.\"}, {\"start\": 463.0, \"end\": 467.0, \"text\": \"So if you're having a hard time waiting for Halloween\"}, {\"start\": 467.0, \"end\": 471.0, \"text\": \"to indulge in chocolate, it's okay to eat a little today.\"}, {\"start\": 475.024, \"end\": 477.099, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories.\"}, {\"start\": 478.0, \"end\": 482.0, \"text\": \"I am Crystal Cousineau. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 482.0, \"end\": 488.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 488.0, \"end\": 495.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "w1CAyTB3wFA": {
    "video_id": "w1CAyTB3wFA",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.11.18 - News in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180112",
    "duration": 563,
    "view_count": 1749,
    "description": "1.11.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Trump slammed for vulgar remarks during DACA meeting \n-Trump’s first presidential exam set for Friday\n-Crews find mudslide victims, search for survivors\n-New guidelines on medicaid work requirements\n-Parents of murdered Pakistani girl say goodbye\n-Eric Clapton reveals hearing loss\n-Will Prince Harry have a best man?\n-Lemurs take over reporter’s live shot\n\nSign1News is the first and only di",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.84, \"end\": 6.7, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.7, \"end\": 9.2, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.2, \"end\": 10.52, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 10.52, \"end\": 13.1, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.82, \"end\": 22.42, \"text\": \"We want to warn you: the language in this story is a bit vulgar and unsuitable for children.\"}, {\"start\": 22.42, \"end\": 25.2, \"text\": \"So please use discretion when viewing it.\"}, {\"start\": 25.2, \"end\": 31.32, \"text\": \"President Trump is being slammed for comments he made today during his meeting with senators\"}, {\"start\": 31.32, \"end\": 38.8, \"text\": \"to discuss DACA, border security and the looming government shutdown.\"}, {\"start\": 38.8, \"end\": 49.84, \"text\": \"According to the Washington Post, Senator Dick Durbin was going through a list of countries\"}, {\"start\": 49.84, \"end\": 52.52, \"text\": \"that received temporary protected status for entering the US.\"}, {\"start\": 52.52, \"end\": 63.38, \"text\": \"When Durbin got to Haiti and African countries, Trump said -- and we're quoting his words exactly:\"}, {\"start\": 63.38, \"end\": 71.24, \"text\": \"\\\"Why do we want all these people from s***hole countries to come here?\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 71.24, \"end\": 80.1, \"text\": \"He added the US should \\\"get more people from countries like Norway.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 80.1, \"end\": 87.3, \"text\": \"Those comments have caused a firestorm of criticism from Democrats who say it proves\"}, {\"start\": 87.3, \"end\": 93.58, \"text\": \"Trump is a racist and has no business being president.\"}, {\"start\": 96.5, \"end\": 101.58, \"text\": \"President Trump is going to the doctor's office Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 101.58, \"end\": 109.72, \"text\": \"The White House says Trump will head to Walter Reed Medical Center for his first known physical\"}, {\"start\": 109.76, \"end\": 117.42, \"text\": \"examination since taking office last year.\"}, {\"start\": 117.42, \"end\": 122.24, \"text\": \"Based on previous presidential exams, the doctor conducting it will make a general assessment\"}, {\"start\": 122.24, \"end\": 128.12, \"text\": \"of the president's health, then provide the public with a readout of the exam once completed.\"}, {\"start\": 128.12, \"end\": 132.86, \"text\": \"However it's unclear how much information will be released.\"}, {\"start\": 132.86, \"end\": 139.36, \"text\": \"Sources say Trump himself will decide what is made public.\"}, {\"start\": 139.36, \"end\": 147.16, \"text\": \"White House officials say Friday's doctor's visit will not include a psychiatric exam.\"}, {\"start\": 150.58, \"end\": 155.42, \"text\": \"More than 500 rescuers are looking for people who disappeared after a massive amount of\"}, {\"start\": 155.42, \"end\": 160.5, \"text\": \"mud and debris devoured sections of Southern California.\"}, {\"start\": 160.54, \"end\": 166.88, \"text\": \"At least 17 deaths of been confirmed and officials fear that number will rise.\"}, {\"start\": 166.88, \"end\": 176.22, \"text\": \"Officials say the mudslides destroyed about 100 homes, while 300 suffered damage.\"}, {\"start\": 176.22, \"end\": 183.44, \"text\": \"The mudslides were caused by Tuesday's heavy rains, nearly 2 inches of rain per hour in\"}, {\"start\": 183.46, \"end\": 186.36, \"text\": \"areas recently scorched by severe wildfires.\"}, {\"start\": 186.36, \"end\": 202.2, \"text\": \"Mud, debris and boulders cover the 101 freeway, which runs through Ventura, Santa Barbara\"}, {\"start\": 202.2, \"end\": 203.98, \"text\": \"and Montecito.\"}, {\"start\": 203.98, \"end\": 208.96, \"text\": \"The California Highway Patrol says parts of the 101 freeway will remain shutdown throughout\"}, {\"start\": 208.96, \"end\": 210.14, \"text\": \"the weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 210.14, \"end\": 216.58, \"text\": \"Crews will try to make the most of the favorable weather conditions.\"}, {\"start\": 216.58, \"end\": 221.9, \"text\": \"Forecasters say there is no precipitation expected over the next seven days.\"}, {\"start\": 224.66, \"end\": 234.04, \"text\": \"Some states could soon require Medicaid recipients to work in order to receive their coverage.\"}, {\"start\": 234.04, \"end\": 241.02, \"text\": \"The Trump administration released guidelines Thursday outlining how states can mandate\"}, {\"start\": 241.02, \"end\": 245.82, \"text\": \"employment for certain Medicaid enrollees.\"}, {\"start\": 245.82, \"end\": 253.16, \"text\": \"So far 10 states have submitted waivers that would allow them to deny care to unemployed\"}, {\"start\": 253.16, \"end\": 255.38, \"text\": \"recipients.\"}, {\"start\": 255.38, \"end\": 269.78, \"text\": \"They are Utah, Arizona, Kansas, Arkansas, Wisconsin, Indiana, Kentucky, North Carolina,\"}, {\"start\": 269.79, \"end\": 273.75, \"text\": \"New Hampshire and Maine.\"}, {\"start\": 273.75, \"end\": 283.24, \"text\": \"Experts say some people have physical or mental health problems that make employment difficult\"}, {\"start\": 283.24, \"end\": 287.8, \"text\": \"but don't qualify for federal disability programs.\"}, {\"start\": 287.8, \"end\": 295.24, \"text\": \"States will be required to fund job-training resources for Medicaid recipients before\"}, {\"start\": 295.24, \"end\": 297.7, \"text\": \"before they can deny coverage.\"}, {\"start\": 297.7, \"end\": 305.02, \"text\": \"Nearly 75 million Americans receive healthcare coverage under the Medicaid program.\"}, {\"start\": 307.96, \"end\": 319.94, \"text\": \"Today the family of a seven-year-old Pakistani girl named Zainab said their goodbyes.\"}, {\"start\": 319.94, \"end\": 327.88, \"text\": \"Zainab was brutally raped, murdered and thrown into a garbage pile last week.\"}, {\"start\": 327.88, \"end\": 332.7, \"text\": \"Surveillance video shows her being led away by an unidentified man.\"}, {\"start\": 332.7, \"end\": 341.4, \"text\": \"Zainab is one of 12 girls who have been killed in the area over the last few months.\"}, {\"start\": 341.4, \"end\": 345.94, \"text\": \"As a result, protests are taking place in several cities across Pakistan.\"}, {\"start\": 345.94, \"end\": 351.34, \"text\": \"Many in the local community say authorities have not done enough to keep their children\"}, {\"start\": 351.34, \"end\": 353.9, \"text\": \"safe.\"}, {\"start\": 353.92, \"end\": 362.34, \"text\": \"Police are offering a $90,000 reward for anyone who can help identify Zainab's killer.\"}, {\"start\": 364.44, \"end\": 377.14, \"text\": \"Rock music legend Eric Clapton says he's losing his hearing.\"}, {\"start\": 377.14, \"end\": 387.0, \"text\": \"Clapton appeared on \\\"BBC Radio Two\\\" this week to discuss his upcoming documentary \\\"Eric\"}, {\"start\": 387.0, \"end\": 392.66, \"text\": \"Clapton: Life in 12 Bars.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 392.66, \"end\": 396.84, \"text\": \"The 72-year-old admitted during the interview that he has tinnitus.\"}, {\"start\": 396.84, \"end\": 402.28, \"text\": \"That's a constant ringing in the ears usually caused by noise-induced hearing loss.\"}, {\"start\": 402.28, \"end\": 406.44, \"text\": \"Clapton is also dealing with weakness and pain in his hands and feet which makes it\"}, {\"start\": 406.44, \"end\": 410.46, \"text\": \"difficult for them to play the guitar.\"}, {\"start\": 410.5, \"end\": 417.4, \"text\": \"Clapton says he intends to continue performing this year and has concerts lined up in New\"}, {\"start\": 417.5, \"end\": 419.28, \"text\": \"York, Los Angeles and Britain.\"}, {\"start\": 419.28, \"end\": 426.22, \"text\": \"The documentary premieres February 10th on Showtime.\"}, {\"start\": 429.92, \"end\": 441.6, \"text\": \"Britain's Prince Harry and actress Meghan Markle are set to tie the knot on May 19th.\"}, {\"start\": 441.6, \"end\": 447.04, \"text\": \"It's assumed that Harry will pick his brother William to be his best man.\"}, {\"start\": 447.04, \"end\": 452.14, \"text\": \"But William says Harry hasn't actually asked him yet.\"}, {\"start\": 452.14, \"end\": 457.8, \"text\": \"Traditionally royal weddings don't even include a best man.\"}, {\"start\": 457.8, \"end\": 463.86, \"text\": \"Instead the groom picks \\\"supporters.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 463.86, \"end\": 473.08, \"text\": \"But if you remember William broke with tradition at his 2011 wedding, picking Harry to be his\"}, {\"start\": 473.1, \"end\": 475.14, \"text\": \"best man.\"}, {\"start\": 475.14, \"end\": 482.54, \"text\": \"And Kate's sister Pippa Middleton served as maid of honor.\"}, {\"start\": 484.14, \"end\": 495.0, \"text\": \"BBC reporter Alex Dunlap's live shot was hijacked by a pack of feisty lemurs.\"}, {\"start\": 495.0, \"end\": 502.08, \"text\": \"Dunlap was trying to report on an animal count at Banham zoo in Norfork England.\"}, {\"start\": 502.08, \"end\": 508.38, \"text\": \"But a pack of lemurs ended up mobbing him instead.\"}, {\"start\": 508.38, \"end\": 513.62, \"text\": \"Ring-tailed lemurs are native to Madagascar.\"}, {\"start\": 513.62, \"end\": 517.76, \"text\": \"They are also highly social creatures.\"}, {\"start\": 517.76, \"end\": 525.82, \"text\": \"The BBC segment was supposed to be an informative report on local zoo business.\"}, {\"start\": 525.82, \"end\": 534.36, \"text\": \"Instead it turned into a wild and hilarious moment that went viral.\"}, {\"start\": 537.32, \"end\": 539.88, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 539.88, \"end\": 541.42, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 541.42, \"end\": 544.18, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 544.2, \"end\": 549.12, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 549.14, \"end\": 556.88, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "wHk7-DjrqxY": {
    "video_id": "wHk7-DjrqxY",
    "title": "W. Virginia lawmakers agree to teacher pay raise (ASL - 3.6.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180307",
    "duration": 54,
    "view_count": 37,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.76, \"end\": 17.4, \"text\": \"Thousands of teachers cheered after lawmakers reached a deal agreeing to give a 5% pay raise\"}, {\"start\": 17.4, \"end\": 22.04, \"text\": \"to all state employees, including teachers and school staff.\"}, {\"start\": 22.04, \"end\": 28.48, \"text\": \"Schools all over the state have been shut down for nine days because of the teachers' strike.\"}, {\"start\": 28.48, \"end\": 37.8, \"text\": \"Both the House and Senate unanimously approved the pay raise and the bill is expected to\"}, {\"start\": 37.8, \"end\": 43.04, \"text\": \"be signed by Governor Jim Justice today.\"}, {\"start\": 43.04, \"end\": 52.74, \"text\": \"A representative for the teachers' union anticipates school will be back in session on Wednesday.\"}]"
  },
  "PNTbO_VrcSI": {
    "video_id": "PNTbO_VrcSI",
    "title": "Mega Millions jackpot at $363M (ASL - 1.2.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180103",
    "duration": 42,
    "view_count": 173,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.0, \"end\": 11.28, \"text\": \"If you're a lottery player and feeling lucky, make sure you buy your Mega Millions ticket tonight.\"}, {\"start\": 11.28, \"end\": 17.28, \"text\": \"The jackpot for tonight's drawing is up to $363 million.\"}, {\"start\": 17.28, \"end\": 25.5, \"text\": \"But did you know Mega Millions officials made a change back in October, giving you more numbers to choose\"}, {\"start\": 25.5, \"end\": 29.48, \"text\": \"therefore making it harder to hit the jackpot?\"}, {\"start\": 29.48, \"end\": 38.1, \"text\": \"That means it's likely no one will win tonight and the jackpot will grow even larger for the next drawing.\"}, {\"start\": 38.1, \"end\": 40.5, \"text\": \"But then again -- tonight just might be your lucky night.\"}]"
  },
  "-Zl-cALyuy8": {
    "video_id": "-Zl-cALyuy8",
    "title": "Sign1News 8.14.19 - News for the Deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20190815",
    "duration": 654,
    "view_count": 1593,
    "description": "TODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Dog owners beware of deadly toxic algae \n-1 in 5 adults uses at least 5 prescription drugs\n-Snapchat unveils sunglasses with 3D effects\n-22 states sue EPA over climate rule rollback\n-Coca-Cola to sell Dasani in cans, bottles\n-Man takes grandma to all 61 national parks!\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in \nAmerican Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and n",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 26.14, \"end\": 27.48, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 27.48, \"end\": 28.96, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 28.96, \"end\": 30.68, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 30.68, \"end\": 33.16, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 37.36, \"end\": 40.96, \"text\": \"We have a warning for dog owners today.\"}, {\"start\": 40.96, \"end\": 48.5, \"text\": \"Toxic algae is suspected in the deaths of four pets in two states.\"}, {\"start\": 48.5, \"end\": 60.36, \"text\": \"Three dogs died in Wilmington, North Carolina after playing in a pond, while another died\"}, {\"start\": 60.36, \"end\": 68.48, \"text\": \"after a swim in Lake Allatoona, Georgia.\"}, {\"start\": 68.48, \"end\": 80.8, \"text\": \"They all died of liver failure caused by ingesting water contaminated with toxic blue-green algae.\"}, {\"start\": 80.8, \"end\": 89.18, \"text\": \"According to the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA), the harmful algae can bloom\"}, {\"start\": 89.18, \"end\": 98.1, \"text\": \"anywhere in the US in both fresh and marine waters as well as backyard pools.\"}, {\"start\": 98.1, \"end\": 112.42, \"text\": \"The toxic algae can be green, blue, red or brown and look like foam or scum on the surface\"}, {\"start\": 112.42, \"end\": 114.98, \"text\": \"of water.\"}, {\"start\": 114.98, \"end\": 118.82, \"text\": \"Often it smells bad but may attract animals.\"}, {\"start\": 118.82, \"end\": 125.78, \"text\": \"If you spot the algae, leave the area immediately.\"}, {\"start\": 125.78, \"end\": 128.7, \"text\": \"Do not let your dog drink or play in the water.\"}, {\"start\": 128.7, \"end\": 132.58, \"text\": \"However if your dog has already been exposed, rinse the animal immediately in fresh, clean\"}, {\"start\": 132.58, \"end\": 134.54, \"text\": \"water wearing gloves to protect yourself as well.\"}, {\"start\": 134.54, \"end\": 138.54, \"text\": \"The toxins are also dangerous to humans.\"}, {\"start\": 138.54, \"end\": 146.76, \"text\": \"Symptoms caused by toxic algae can begin within fifteen minutes or take several days.\"}, {\"start\": 146.76, \"end\": 152.66, \"text\": \"They include diarrhea or vomiting, weakness or staggering, drooling, difficulty breathing\"}, {\"start\": 152.66, \"end\": 153.64, \"text\": \"and seizures.\"}, {\"start\": 153.64, \"end\": 157.08, \"text\": \"If your dog displays any of these symptoms after making contact with water, take it to\"}, {\"start\": 157.08, \"end\": 158.96, \"text\": \"the vet immediately.\"}, {\"start\": 161.92, \"end\": 166.98, \"text\": \"How many prescription drugs do you take?\"}, {\"start\": 166.98, \"end\": 176.8, \"text\": \"If it's a lot, you're not alone.\"}, {\"start\": 176.8, \"end\": 186.46, \"text\": \"A new Centers for Disease Control study shows most adults aged 40 to 79 took at least one\"}, {\"start\": 186.46, \"end\": 189.92, \"text\": \"prescription drug in the past month.\"}, {\"start\": 189.92, \"end\": 195.78, \"text\": \"One in five took at least five.\"}, {\"start\": 195.78, \"end\": 198.4, \"text\": \"So what pills are everyone popping?\"}, {\"start\": 198.4, \"end\": 207.0, \"text\": \"For the younger half of the group, it's mostly antidepressants, ACE inhibitors - which are\"}, {\"start\": 207.0, \"end\": 214.4, \"text\": \"used to lower blood pressure and treat migraines - and cholesterol-lowering drugs.\"}, {\"start\": 214.4, \"end\": 222.76, \"text\": \"For the older set, cholesterol-lowering drugs continue to be a favorite but also antidiabetic\"}, {\"start\": 222.76, \"end\": 229.96, \"text\": \"medications and beta blockers - another class of drugs used to lower blood pressure.\"}, {\"start\": 229.96, \"end\": 239.96, \"text\": \"The study also shows women take more prescription drugs than men.\"}, {\"start\": 242.18, \"end\": 254.16, \"text\": \"Snapchat's parent company, Snap, has unveiled redesigned \\\"Spectacles\\\" sunglasses with 3D effects.\"}, {\"start\": 254.16, \"end\": 262.82, \"text\": \"Spectacles 3, the latest version of Snapchat's video recording sunglasses, also comes with\"}, {\"start\": 262.82, \"end\": 266.56, \"text\": \"an eye-popping price tag.\"}, {\"start\": 266.56, \"end\": 275.44, \"text\": \"At $380, it's more than double the cost of its previous version.\"}, {\"start\": 275.44, \"end\": 283.32, \"text\": \"Less than three years ago, Snapchat's first pair initially sold in vending machines and\"}, {\"start\": 283.32, \"end\": 285.38, \"text\": \"became a viral hit.\"}, {\"start\": 285.38, \"end\": 296.98, \"text\": \"However the hype fizzled and the company had to take a nearly $40 million write-down for\"}, {\"start\": 296.98, \"end\": 298.56, \"text\": \"excessive inventory.\"}, {\"start\": 298.56, \"end\": 306.44, \"text\": \"Snap said Spectacles 3 is a limited edition product and it will make less of the new sunglasses\"}, {\"start\": 306.44, \"end\": 308.16, \"text\": \"than it has in the past.\"}, {\"start\": 308.16, \"end\": 316.06, \"text\": \"The device is available for preorder now but it won't ship until fall.\"}, {\"start\": 318.34, \"end\": 325.76, \"text\": \"A coalition of 22 states and some cities are suing the Environmental Protection Agency\"}, {\"start\": 325.76, \"end\": 334.94, \"text\": \"over its rollback of an Obama-era climate rule involving powerplants.\"}, {\"start\": 334.94, \"end\": 342.76, \"text\": \"It has the potential to become a historic court case that may reduce states' ability\"}, {\"start\": 342.76, \"end\": 351.44, \"text\": \"to choose sources of energy with lower greenhouse gas emissions.\"}, {\"start\": 351.44, \"end\": 355.94, \"text\": \"The federal lawsuit challenges the EPA in its efforts to rollback restrictions on coal\"}, {\"start\": 355.94, \"end\": 358.54, \"text\": \"burning power plants.\"}, {\"start\": 358.54, \"end\": 365.92, \"text\": \"It claims a change undercuts efforts to reduce greenhouse gas emissions and disregards the\"}, {\"start\": 365.92, \"end\": 372.88, \"text\": \"federal Clean Air Act.\"}, {\"start\": 372.88, \"end\": 382.96, \"text\": \"The rule change is designed to make good on President Trump's campaign promise to revive\"}, {\"start\": 382.96, \"end\": 385.88, \"text\": \"the nation's coal industry.\"}, {\"start\": 385.88, \"end\": 391.86, \"text\": \"And eliminates what had been an aggressive effort to reduce the energy sector's carbon\"}, {\"start\": 391.86, \"end\": 393.1, \"text\": \"footprint.\"}, {\"start\": 393.1, \"end\": 401.66, \"text\": \"However the EPA is defending the revised rule, saying it believes it will be upheld in the courts.\"}, {\"start\": 401.66, \"end\": 409.84, \"text\": \"This is the latest pushback by states accusing the Trump administration of endangering the\"}, {\"start\": 409.84, \"end\": 411.4, \"text\": \"environment with his policies.\"}, {\"start\": 411.4, \"end\": 417.22, \"text\": \"Four the states involved in the lawsuit are Wisconsin, Michigan, Pennsylvania and North\"}, {\"start\": 417.22, \"end\": 424.98, \"text\": \"Carolina, which Trump won in the 2016 election.\"}, {\"start\": 427.5, \"end\": 434.2, \"text\": \"The next bottle of water Coca-Cola sells you as you might come in a can.\"}, {\"start\": 434.2, \"end\": 444.7, \"text\": \"Starting next year, Coke plans to start offering its Dasani water in aluminum cans and bottles\"}, {\"start\": 444.7, \"end\": 447.56, \"text\": \"to make it more environmentally friendly.\"}, {\"start\": 447.56, \"end\": 455.06, \"text\": \"The company hopes to collect and recycle the equivalent of every bottle or can it sells\"}, {\"start\": 455.06, \"end\": 456.5, \"text\": \"by 2030.\"}, {\"start\": 456.5, \"end\": 462.34, \"text\": \"That's a pretty lofty goal considering the soft drink giant produced 3.3 million tons\"}, {\"start\": 462.34, \"end\": 464.64, \"text\": \"of plastic in 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 464.64, \"end\": 473.24, \"text\": \"Aluminum is easier to recycle than plastic, so moving customers away from plastic will\"}, {\"start\": 473.24, \"end\": 475.0, \"text\": \"likely help.\"}, {\"start\": 475.0, \"end\": 482.14, \"text\": \"Dasani will still be available in plastic bottles but they'll be lighter weight.\"}, {\"start\": 482.14, \"end\": 489.28, \"text\": \"Coke also has plans for a new bottle made with up to 50 percent recycled plastic and\"}, {\"start\": 489.28, \"end\": 493.58, \"text\": \"plant-based materials.\"}, {\"start\": 495.76, \"end\": 501.68, \"text\": \"Eighty-one-year-old Ohio grandmother Joy Ryan is on a mission to visit every national park\"}, {\"start\": 501.68, \"end\": 503.68, \"text\": \"in the country.\"}, {\"start\": 503.68, \"end\": 508.74, \"text\": \"She's got more than 31 to go and just over a year to do it.\"}, {\"start\": 508.74, \"end\": 519.5, \"text\": \"Ryan wants to see all sixty-one parks before she turned 90.\"}, {\"start\": 519.5, \"end\": 527.76, \"text\": \"She's got plenty of support in a very special travel companions � her grandson Brad.\"}, {\"start\": 527.76, \"end\": 529.66, \"text\": \"It was actually his idea.\"}, {\"start\": 529.66, \"end\": 536.84, \"text\": \"When he told her about a trip he took hiking the Appalachian trail while in veterinary\"}, {\"start\": 536.84, \"end\": 542.0, \"text\": \"school, she expressed regret at never having done anything like that.\"}, {\"start\": 542.0, \"end\": 549.42, \"text\": \"All her kids were grown, her husband had died twenty years ago and she had never seen a\"}, {\"start\": 549.42, \"end\": 551.68, \"text\": \"mountain.\"}, {\"start\": 551.68, \"end\": 563.3, \"text\": \"So in 2015, he took her to Great Smoky Mountains National Park and they have been traveling\"}, {\"start\": 563.3, \"end\": 565.22, \"text\": \"together ever since.\"}, {\"start\": 565.22, \"end\": 572.02, \"text\": \"Brad says his grandmother knows she is seeing these amazing sights for the first and last\"}, {\"start\": 572.02, \"end\": 581.84, \"text\": \"time and watching her take it all in has changed the way he lives.\"}, {\"start\": 581.84, \"end\": 592.04, \"text\": \"You can follow their adventures on Instagram or Facebook. Look for \\\"Grandma Joy's Road Trip.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 592.04, \"end\": 598.72, \"text\": \"And Grandma Joy's story is a great reminder for all of us: take the time to really enjoy\"}, {\"start\": 598.72, \"end\": 600.68, \"text\": \"life while you have time.\"}, {\"start\": 600.68, \"end\": 606.98, \"text\": \"Don't let fear, disabilities, lack of money or negative people stop you from doing the\"}, {\"start\": 606.98, \"end\": 615.02, \"text\": \"things you want to do and achieving the goals you want to achieve.\"}, {\"start\": 615.02, \"end\": 620.48, \"text\": \"And you know what -- why not start today?\"}, {\"start\": 625.56, \"end\": 627.24, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 627.24, \"end\": 628.46, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 628.46, \"end\": 630.46, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 630.46, \"end\": 638.02, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our\"}, {\"start\": 638.02, \"end\": 639.9, \"text\": \"app too.\"}, {\"start\": 639.9, \"end\": 645.3, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your life.\"}]"
  },
  "sqJcHZ4bYPw": {
    "video_id": "sqJcHZ4bYPw",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.1.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180402",
    "duration": 619,
    "view_count": 1607,
    "description": "4.1.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-CVS sued for revealing HIV status of 6,000 patients\n-NY Law: domestic abusers must surrender guns\n-Stephon Clark protester struck by police car\n-Don’t fall for these April Fool’s Day jokes\n-Retiring trooper makes emotional final radio call\n-Weekend box office\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable org",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.1, \"end\": 9.78, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.78, \"end\": 12.16, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.16, \"end\": 13.5, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.5, \"end\": 16.92, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.4, \"end\": 29.96, \"text\": \"CVS Health is being sued for allegedly revealing the HIV status of 6,000 patients in Ohio.\"}, {\"start\": 29.96, \"end\": 34.92, \"text\": \"The complaint was filed in federal court on March 21.\"}, {\"start\": 34.92, \"end\": 43.1, \"text\": \"The patients in question were part of Ohio's HIV drug resistance program.\"}, {\"start\": 43.1, \"end\": 50.76, \"text\": \"The lawsuit claims that CVS mailed letters last year where patients' HIV status could\"}, {\"start\": 50.76, \"end\": 56.74, \"text\": \"be seen through the envelope window.\"}, {\"start\": 56.74, \"end\": 68.7, \"text\": \"Fiserv, the company that CVS hired to mail the letters, is also named in the lawsuit.\"}, {\"start\": 68.7, \"end\": 80.24, \"text\": \"In a statement to CNN, CVS health said the envelope window was intended to show a reference\"}, {\"start\": 80.24, \"end\": 88.52, \"text\": \"code for the assistance program and not the patients' health status.\"}, {\"start\": 88.52, \"end\": 101.32, \"text\": \"The plaintiffs are seeking class action status and a jury trial.\"}, {\"start\": 105.16, \"end\": 115.52, \"text\": \"Lawmakers in New York State have passed legislation that would allow judges to force people arraigned\"}, {\"start\": 115.52, \"end\": 124.48, \"text\": \"on domestic abuse charges to surrender all of their firearms.\"}, {\"start\": 124.48, \"end\": 134.38, \"text\": \"New York Governor Andrew Cuomo said previously, domestic abusers in the state only had to\"}, {\"start\": 134.38, \"end\": 150.68, \"text\": \"give up their handguns, but they got to keep other firearms.\"}, {\"start\": 150.68, \"end\": 157.68, \"text\": \"Cuomo says he hopes the legislation will make New York safer and stronger, as well as break\"}, {\"start\": 157.68, \"end\": 163.38, \"text\": \"the link between domestic abuse and gun violence.\"}, {\"start\": 166.24, \"end\": 179.22, \"text\": \"Large crowds took to the Sacramento streets Saturday night as the protests continued in\"}, {\"start\": 179.22, \"end\": 187.24, \"text\": \"the shooting death of Stephon Clark.\"}, {\"start\": 187.24, \"end\": 192.9, \"text\": \"He was unarmed and standing in his grandmother's backyard when he was shot killed by police\"}, {\"start\": 192.9, \"end\": 195.66, \"text\": \"on March 18.\"}, {\"start\": 195.66, \"end\": 203.38, \"text\": \"Protests have been peaceful up to this point.\"}, {\"start\": 203.38, \"end\": 213.8, \"text\": \"But observers say they can sense the tension between protesters and police intensifying.\"}, {\"start\": 213.8, \"end\": 226.9, \"text\": \"Last night at a vigil for Clark a woman suffered minor injuries after being struck by a Sacramento\"}, {\"start\": 226.9, \"end\": 231.94, \"text\": \"County Sheriff's deputy's vehicle.\"}, {\"start\": 231.94, \"end\": 244.62, \"text\": \"Video filmed Saturday night captured the moment the Sheriff's SUV hit the woman and then pulls away.\"}, {\"start\": 256.42, \"end\": 266.32, \"text\": \"The Sheriff spokesman said the deputy's vehicle had scratches, dents and a shattered rear\"}, {\"start\": 266.32, \"end\": 272.14, \"text\": \"window caused by vandals in the crowd.\"}, {\"start\": 274.54, \"end\": 279.56, \"text\": \"The California Highway Patrol says it is investigating.\"}, {\"start\": 282.0, \"end\": 287.96, \"text\": \"It is not only Easter, is also April Fools' Day.\"}, {\"start\": 287.98, \"end\": 294.92, \"text\": \"And this year a few corporations got in on the April Fools' Day pranking.\"}, {\"start\": 294.92, \"end\": 303.36, \"text\": \"So be careful and don't fall for these fake commercials.\"}, {\"start\": 303.36, \"end\": 311.66, \"text\": \"Burger King posted a video announcing the Chocolate Whopper, which has a chocolate cake\"}, {\"start\": 311.66, \"end\": 324.3, \"text\": \"bun, raspberry syrup instead of ketchup and white chocolate rings instead of onions.\"}, {\"start\": 324.3, \"end\": 332.4, \"text\": \"Auntie Anne's pretzels sent out a press release for \\\"Heavenly Scent\\\" essential pretzel oils.\"}, {\"start\": 332.4, \"end\": 341.66, \"text\": \"It says you can smell like a freshly baked, salty or cinnamon twist pretzel.\"}, {\"start\": 341.66, \"end\": 351.1, \"text\": \"But a line at the bottom of the press release revealed it as fake news.\"}, {\"start\": 351.1, \"end\": 356.32, \"text\": \"The company says: \\\"We recommend consuming pretzels, not rubbing them on your skin and\"}, {\"start\": 356.32, \"end\": 361.34, \"text\": \"hair as a substitute.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 361.34, \"end\": 368.66, \"text\": \"Pindrop, a phone and voice communication security company, released this ad for \\\"tongue printing\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 368.66, \"end\": 370.42, \"text\": \"technology.\"}, {\"start\": 370.42, \"end\": 374.38, \"text\": \"It's top knot security.\"}, {\"start\": 374.4, \"end\": 380.68, \"text\": \"Just lick your phone and you're logged in.\"}, {\"start\": 380.68, \"end\": 388.5, \"text\": \"T-Mobile went all out this year, introducing the world's first smart shoe phone called the\"}, {\"start\": 388.5, \"end\": 392.3, \"text\": \"T-Mobile Sidekicks.\"}, {\"start\": 392.3, \"end\": 400.94, \"text\": \"The soles of the shoes turn into speakers, the shoe laces are retractable earbuds and\"}, {\"start\": 400.94, \"end\": 405.02, \"text\": \"there's a camera in the toe.\"}, {\"start\": 405.02, \"end\": 413.86, \"text\": \"The smartphone technology is not real, but if you want the actual pink footwear you can\"}, {\"start\": 413.86, \"end\": 420.54, \"text\": \"preorder them at Bemagenta.com before April 15.\"}, {\"start\": 423.82, \"end\": 433.04, \"text\": \"Arizona trooper Mark Gilberg began his law enforcement career with the Department of\"}, {\"start\": 433.04, \"end\": 440.92, \"text\": \"Public Safety on March 11, 1981.\"}, {\"start\": 440.92, \"end\": 447.04, \"text\": \"On Thursday the 37-year veteran signed off for the last time.\"}, {\"start\": 447.04, \"end\": 455.02, \"text\": \"And his emotional final radio call is making the rounds on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 455.02, \"end\": 460.98, \"text\": \"Watch as Gilberg calls into dispatch for the last time.\"}, {\"start\": 461.92, \"end\": 466.22, \"text\": \"I just wanted to thank everyone for everything they've ever done.\"}, {\"start\": 466.22, \"end\": 470.48, \"text\": \"It's been an honor and privilege and a great career.\"}, {\"start\": 470.48, \"end\": 472.78, \"text\": \"It's been a great adventure.\"}, {\"start\": 472.94, \"end\": 479.52, \"text\": \"I thank everyone that's ever helped me and as I said it's been an honor and a great pleasure\"}, {\"start\": 479.52, \"end\": 482.96, \"text\": \"to serve in this great department and to work with all of you fine people.\"}, {\"start\": 483.8, \"end\": 490.68, \"text\": \"This is 1-5-2, badge 2988, 39 years and three weeks later.\"}, {\"start\": 490.68, \"end\": 492.42, \"text\": \"It's been a great ride.\"}, {\"start\": 492.42, \"end\": 494.58, \"text\": \"Thank you very much and keep smiling.\"}, {\"start\": 496.38, \"end\": 501.08, \"text\": \"(radio dispatch) Unit 1-5-2, thank you for your service too.\"}, {\"start\": 501.08, \"end\": 506.48, \"text\": \"We appreciate everything that you have done.\"}, {\"start\": 506.48, \"end\": 508.72, \"text\": \"And congratulations on your tenure.\"}, {\"start\": 508.72, \"end\": 510.32, \"text\": \"That's awesome.\"}, {\"start\": 510.46, \"end\": 512.5, \"text\": \"You have good luck in your future endeavors.\"}, {\"start\": 512.66, \"end\": 514.32, \"text\": \"We appreciate it.\"}, {\"start\": 514.88, \"end\": 517.2, \"text\": \"10-4, 10-7.\"}, {\"start\": 518.08, \"end\": 523.8, \"text\": \"(radio dispatch) 1-5-2, 10-4 at 16:07.\"}, {\"start\": 524.76, \"end\": 532.04, \"text\": \"(sounds of crying)\"}, {\"start\": 532.56, \"end\": 541.88, \"text\": \"Here's a quick recap of this weekend's box office winners.\"}, {\"start\": 541.88, \"end\": 552.0, \"text\": \"Steven Spielberg's \\\"Ready Player One\\\" topped the box office, giving the director his biggest\"}, {\"start\": 552.0, \"end\": 556.46, \"text\": \"weekend opening in a decade.\"}, {\"start\": 556.46, \"end\": 566.68, \"text\": \"The film made just over $41 million over the weekend and just over $53 million if you included\"}, {\"start\": 566.68, \"end\": 568.76, \"text\": \"receipts from its debut Thursday night.\"}, {\"start\": 568.76, \"end\": 576.68, \"text\": \"Tyler Perry's latest movie \\\"Acrimony\\\" took the number two spot.\"}, {\"start\": 576.68, \"end\": 582.38, \"text\": \"It took in just over $17 million.\"}, {\"start\": 582.38, \"end\": 586.2, \"text\": \"And in the third spot, \\\"Black Panther.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 586.2, \"end\": 589.52, \"text\": \"It took in just over $11 million at the box office.\"}, {\"start\": 592.72, \"end\": 595.68, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 595.68, \"end\": 597.0, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 597.0, \"end\": 599.88, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 599.88, \"end\": 605.62, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 605.62, \"end\": 612.22, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "dF-8sngLwcU": {
    "video_id": "dF-8sngLwcU",
    "title": "Russia expels U.S. diplomats in retaliation (ASL - 3.29.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180330",
    "duration": 107,
    "view_count": 293,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.5, \"end\": 11.12, \"text\": \"Earlier this week Washington expelled 60 Russian diplomats.\"}, {\"start\": 11.14, \"end\": 29.7, \"text\": \"It was part of a global response to the poisoning of a former Russian double agent and his daughter\"}, {\"start\": 29.7, \"end\": 31.38, \"text\": \"in England.\"}, {\"start\": 31.38, \"end\": 58.96, \"text\": \"UK authorities openly blamed Russia for using a military-grade nerve agent for the poisoning\"}, {\"start\": 58.96, \"end\": 63.38, \"text\": \"on March 4.\"}, {\"start\": 63.38, \"end\": 74.1, \"text\": \"Today Russia retaliated by expelling 60 US diplomats and ordered the closure of the US\"}, {\"start\": 74.1, \"end\": 81.92, \"text\": \"consulate in St. Petersburg.\"}, {\"start\": 81.92, \"end\": 89.1, \"text\": \"Russian officials say the US diplomats have to be out of the country by April 5.\"}, {\"start\": 89.12, \"end\": 101.04, \"text\": \"Russia denies responsibility for the poisoning and President Vladimir Putin has dismissed\"}, {\"start\": 101.04, \"end\": 105.2, \"text\": \"it as \\\"delirium.\\\"\"}]"
  },
  "DFwQQL6_YZ8": {
    "video_id": "DFwQQL6_YZ8",
    "title": "Update: White House shooter dies (ASL - 3.4.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180305",
    "duration": 57,
    "view_count": 207,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.18, \"end\": 6.98, \"text\": \"The man who shot himself just outside the White House Saturday morning has died from\"}, {\"start\": 6.98, \"end\": 8.68, \"text\": \"his injuries.\"}, {\"start\": 8.68, \"end\": 15.78, \"text\": \"According to the Secret Service, the incident happened just outside the north fence of the\"}, {\"start\": 15.78, \"end\": 17.16, \"text\": \"building.\"}, {\"start\": 17.2, \"end\": 20.9, \"text\": \"Officials say a man pulled out a gun and fired several rounds.\"}, {\"start\": 20.9, \"end\": 27.58, \"text\": \"None of the shots appeared to be directed at the White House and no Secret Service officers\"}, {\"start\": 27.59, \"end\": 29.199, \"text\": \"returned fire.\"}, {\"start\": 29.2, \"end\": 33.0, \"text\": \"The shooter then turned the gun on himself shot himself in the head.\"}, {\"start\": 33.0, \"end\": 41.14, \"text\": \"Investigators say they did not find a suicide note on the scene but they recovered a book\"}, {\"start\": 41.14, \"end\": 46.36, \"text\": \"that contained some incoherent sentences.\"}, {\"start\": 46.36, \"end\": 53.78, \"text\": \"President Trump and First Lady Melania Trump were at Mar-a-Lago in Florida at the time\"}, {\"start\": 53.8, \"end\": 56.58, \"text\": \"of the incident.\"}]"
  },
  "03ky2gf59Hw": {
    "video_id": "03ky2gf59Hw",
    "title": "Stoplight shootout caught on camera (ASL - 1.24.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180125",
    "duration": 133,
    "view_count": 208,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.66, \"end\": 14.88, \"text\": \"Police in Pensacola, Florida are searching for a man involved in a shoot out at a stoplight.\"}, {\"start\": 14.96, \"end\": 29.48, \"text\": \"It happened around noon on Monday at the intersection of Fairfield Drive and W Street.\"}, {\"start\": 29.48, \"end\": 48.12, \"text\": \"Police say the driver of a silver Lexus pulled up at a stoplight and exchanged gunfire with\"}, {\"start\": 48.12, \"end\": 49.88, \"text\": \"someone in a gold Toyota.\"}, {\"start\": 49.88, \"end\": 52.58, \"text\": \"And it was all caught on camera.\"}, {\"start\": 52.64, \"end\": 53.64, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 73.8, \"end\": 82.72, \"text\": \"There were two children in the Toyota but amazingly no one was hurt in the shootout.\"}, {\"start\": 82.72, \"end\": 90.24, \"text\": \"Police later spotted the Toyota and arrested the suspect after a brief chase.\"}, {\"start\": 90.24, \"end\": 94.95, \"text\": \"But they are still looking for the driver of the Lexus.\"}, {\"start\": 94.96, \"end\": 104.84, \"text\": \"It has a Florida tag number H-V-R-G-6-9.\"}, {\"start\": 104.84, \"end\": 115.48, \"text\": \"Anyone with information on the shooting is asked to call the Escambia County Sheriff's\"}, {\"start\": 115.48, \"end\": 132.2, \"text\": \"office at 850-436-9620 or Crimestoppers at 850-433-7867.\"}]"
  },
  "i-F6l3YmS1I": {
    "video_id": "i-F6l3YmS1I",
    "title": "Legalizing pot could help opioid crisis (ASL - 4.3.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180404",
    "duration": 110,
    "view_count": 145,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.64, \"end\": 18.06, \"text\": \"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention says on average, 115 Americans die every day\"}, {\"start\": 18.06, \"end\": 21.35, \"text\": \"from an opioid overdose.\"}, {\"start\": 21.35, \"end\": 37.91, \"text\": \"But according to two new studies, marijuana could help curb America's opioid epidemic.\"}, {\"start\": 37.91, \"end\": 61.26, \"text\": \"Researchers compared opioid prescription patterns in states with and without medical cannabis\"}, {\"start\": 61.26, \"end\": 73.3, \"text\": \"laws and found that states with medical marijuana laws had 2.2 million fewer daily doses of\"}, {\"start\": 73.3, \"end\": 76.75, \"text\": \"opioids prescribed per year.\"}, {\"start\": 76.75, \"end\": 94.659, \"text\": \"Also opioid prescriptions under Medicaid dropped by 5.88% in states with medical marijuana.\"}, {\"start\": 94.66, \"end\": 105.02, \"text\": \"Just like opioids, marijuana has been shown to be effective in treating chronic pain and\"}, {\"start\": 105.02, \"end\": 109.24, \"text\": \"other conditions.\"}]"
  },
  "rGN0WjdtTTY": {
    "video_id": "rGN0WjdtTTY",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.29.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171229",
    "duration": 506,
    "view_count": 628,
    "description": "December 29, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-DEADLY BRONX FIRE\n-RETIREMENT HOME BEATING CAUGHT ON CAMERA\n-JERUSALEM PAYS TRIBUTE TO PRESIDENT TRUMP\n-APPLE DROPS BATTERY PRICES, APOLOGIZES FOR ISSUES\n-SERENA WILLIAMS RETURNS TO TENNIS SATURDAY\n-HOW TO PREVENT NEW YEAR'S HANGOVER\n-PEOPLE THROW BOILING WATER INTO FREEZING AIR\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-li",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.28, \"end\": 9.24, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.24, \"end\": 11.5, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.5, \"end\": 13.12, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 13.12, \"end\": 15.84, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.6, \"end\": 26.78, \"text\": \"At least 12 people were killed in a fire Thursday night at an apartment building in the Bronx\"}, {\"start\": 26.78, \"end\": 30.14, \"text\": \"borough of New York City.\"}, {\"start\": 30.14, \"end\": 33.68, \"text\": \"Three of the 12 people killed were children.\"}, {\"start\": 33.68, \"end\": 39.02, \"text\": \"Fire officials say that the flame started in a first floor unit, where a three-year-old\"}, {\"start\": 39.02, \"end\": 43.5, \"text\": \"boy was playing with the burners on the stove.\"}, {\"start\": 43.5, \"end\": 48.98, \"text\": \"His mother noticed when the boy screamed.\"}, {\"start\": 48.98, \"end\": 51.0, \"text\": \"But when the mother fled the burning apartment with the boy, she made the mistake of leaving\"}, {\"start\": 51.0, \"end\": 52.12, \"text\": \"the apartment door open.\"}, {\"start\": 52.12, \"end\": 57.62, \"text\": \"That sucked the flames out of the apartment and quickly spread up the stairs of the building.\"}, {\"start\": 57.62, \"end\": 64.12, \"text\": \"New York Mayor Bill DeBlasio is calling this the worst fire tragedy in the city in at least\"}, {\"start\": 64.12, \"end\": 69.68, \"text\": \"25 years.\"}, {\"start\": 71.68, \"end\": 82.14, \"text\": \"A retirement home in Florida has shut down after video surfaced of a resident mercilessly\"}, {\"start\": 82.14, \"end\": 86.82, \"text\": \"beating another resident.\"}, {\"start\": 86.82, \"end\": 93.08, \"text\": \"The video was captured by the retirement home surveillance system.\"}, {\"start\": 93.08, \"end\": 95.92, \"text\": \"In the video, a 52-year-old man is seen punching an 86-year-old man.\"}, {\"start\": 95.92, \"end\": 98.6, \"text\": \"The older man falls to the floor.\"}, {\"start\": 98.6, \"end\": 101.98, \"text\": \"When he gets back up to confront the younger man, the younger man knocks him to the ground\"}, {\"start\": 101.98, \"end\": 106.6, \"text\": \"again and punches him more than 50 times while the older man lay curled up on the floor.\"}, {\"start\": 106.6, \"end\": 108.8, \"text\": \"We have the disturbing video. Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 152.48, \"end\": 158.8, \"text\": \"Police say it all started when the younger man accused the older man of eating his cupcake.\"}, {\"start\": 158.8, \"end\": 161.36, \"text\": \"The older man had to be hospitalized.\"}, {\"start\": 161.36, \"end\": 168.72, \"text\": \"Police say the man who beat him will not be charged because of his limited mental capacity.\"}, {\"start\": 168.72, \"end\": 174.16, \"text\": \"He was removed from the facility temporarily but was later allowed to return with one-on-one\"}, {\"start\": 174.16, \"end\": 177.04, \"text\": \"supervision.\"}, {\"start\": 179.12, \"end\": 185.44, \"text\": \"Less than a month after President Trump recognized Jerusalem as Israel's capital, cities across\"}, {\"start\": 185.44, \"end\": 195.6, \"text\": \"the country are racing to dedicate projects to him.\"}, {\"start\": 195.92, \"end\": 204.34, \"text\": \"Israel has praised Trump as a hero even though the majority of the world overwhelmingly rejected\"}, {\"start\": 204.34, \"end\": 208.84, \"text\": \"Trump's decision.\"}, {\"start\": 208.84, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"Some street names are being changed to \\\"President Donald Trump Street.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 217.0, \"end\": 224.54, \"text\": \"A park in northern Israel will be called \\\"Donald Trump Park.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 224.54, \"end\": 231.86, \"text\": \"But the biggest project is a new high-speed rail project.\"}, {\"start\": 231.86, \"end\": 239.04, \"text\": \"Once it's completed it will be called \\\"Donald J. Trump Station.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 240.8, \"end\": 245.92, \"text\": \"Apple extends an apology to its customers.\"}, {\"start\": 246.02, \"end\": 254.04, \"text\": \"The California-based company admits its most recent software update can cause problems\"}, {\"start\": 254.04, \"end\": 258.05, \"text\": \"for some iPhones.\"}, {\"start\": 258.05, \"end\": 265.39, \"text\": \"In a statement released Thursday, Apple said this update slowed older phones to help extend\"}, {\"start\": 265.39, \"end\": 266.86, \"text\": \"battery life.\"}, {\"start\": 266.86, \"end\": 273.82, \"text\": \"Some say this was a trick to get into customers' wallets.\"}, {\"start\": 273.82, \"end\": 278.12, \"text\": \"A number of class action lawsuits have been filed against Apple in California, Illinois\"}, {\"start\": 278.12, \"end\": 280.32, \"text\": \"and New York.\"}, {\"start\": 280.32, \"end\": 288.8, \"text\": \"IPhones owners say Apple's lack of an explanation caused many users to purchase newer, more\"}, {\"start\": 288.8, \"end\": 291.1, \"text\": \"expensive products.\"}, {\"start\": 291.1, \"end\": 296.78, \"text\": \"Apple's statement said: \\\"We have never and would never do anything to intentionally shorten\"}, {\"start\": 296.78, \"end\": 300.32, \"text\": \"the life of any Apple product or degrade the user experience to drive customer upgrades.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 300.32, \"end\": 305.12, \"text\": \"In addition to the apology, Apple is slicing battery costs to $29 starting next month.\"}, {\"start\": 305.12, \"end\": 309.32, \"text\": \"But it will return to its usual $79 price tag in 2019.\"}, {\"start\": 311.36, \"end\": 321.84, \"text\": \"Tennis star Serena Williams is getting ready for her big comeback.\"}, {\"start\": 321.84, \"end\": 326.84, \"text\": \"On Saturday she is scheduled to play in an exhibition event in Abu Dhabi in the United\"}, {\"start\": 326.84, \"end\": 335.64, \"text\": \"Arab Emirates.\"}, {\"start\": 335.64, \"end\": 345.12, \"text\": \"This will be her first time back on the court since giving birth to her daughter, Alexis.\"}, {\"start\": 345.12, \"end\": 353.52, \"text\": \"Williams' last tournament was 11 months ago when she won the Australian Open.\"}, {\"start\": 353.56, \"end\": 356.76, \"text\": \"She was already two months pregnant at the time.\"}, {\"start\": 358.28, \"end\": 364.68, \"text\": \"If your New Year's Eve plans include drinking alcohol, we have some tips on how to avoid\"}, {\"start\": 364.68, \"end\": 367.4, \"text\": \"that New Year's day hangover.\"}, {\"start\": 367.4, \"end\": 370.36, \"text\": \"First hydrate.\"}, {\"start\": 370.6, \"end\": 382.68, \"text\": \"Try drinking electrolyte-rich water in between alcoholic beverages.\"}, {\"start\": 382.68, \"end\": 389.76, \"text\": \"Second eat a banana or any potassium-rich foods after drinking.\"}, {\"start\": 389.76, \"end\": 393.12, \"text\": \"It will help you fight fatigue.\"}, {\"start\": 393.12, \"end\": 399.88, \"text\": \"Third don't drink on an empty stomach.\"}, {\"start\": 399.88, \"end\": 405.0, \"text\": \"Eating first will slow the alcohol from being absorbed by the body too fast.\"}, {\"start\": 405.0, \"end\": 412.8, \"text\": \"And finally, according to the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, alcohol affects\"}, {\"start\": 412.8, \"end\": 418.36, \"text\": \"every organ in the body.\"}, {\"start\": 418.36, \"end\": 423.76, \"text\": \"So drink moderately.\"}, {\"start\": 426.36, \"end\": 428.76, \"text\": \"Check out this amazing video.\"}, {\"start\": 433.56, \"end\": 449.88, \"text\": \"It's so cold in New Hampshire right now a man threw boiling water into the air and it\"}, {\"start\": 449.88, \"end\": 451.68, \"text\": \"froze before it hit the ground.\"}, {\"start\": 451.68, \"end\": 458.84, \"text\": \"Forecasters say the windchill will be as low as 35 degrees below zero this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 458.84, \"end\": 464.88, \"text\": \"Not only is that enough to freeze boiling water, it can also cause frostbite in as little\"}, {\"start\": 464.88, \"end\": 467.28, \"text\": \"as 10 minutes.\"}, {\"start\": 467.32, \"end\": 473.04, \"text\": \"Forecasters say the weather will \\\"warm\\\" up a bit by next Thursday.\"}, {\"start\": 473.16, \"end\": 475.84, \"text\": \"That's when it is forecast to reach -2 degrees.\"}, {\"start\": 477.9, \"end\": 480.6, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 480.6, \"end\": 481.76, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 481.82, \"end\": 484.8, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 484.8, \"end\": 490.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 490.0, \"end\": 496.84, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "4rWrNpTI7HE": {
    "video_id": "4rWrNpTI7HE",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.20.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171221",
    "duration": 565,
    "view_count": 1001,
    "description": "December 20, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-TRUMP CELEBRATES FIRST LEGISLATIVE VICTORY\n-GOP SCRAMBLES FOR SHUTDOWN SOLUTION\n-ACID ATTACKS ON THE RISE IN LONDON\n-DRAMATIC VIDEO OF OFFICER BEING DRAGGED BY SUSPECT\n-TURTLE ENTANGLED IN BUNDLES OF COCAINE\n-LADY GAGA REVEALS LAS VEGAS RESIDENCY\n-2ND GEORGIA DOME IMPLOSION\n\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line n",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.16, \"end\": 9.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.0, \"end\": 10.48, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.48, \"end\": 11.6, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.6, \"end\": 14.02, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.82, \"end\": 22.84, \"text\": \"The Trump administration is celebrating its first major legislative victory.\"}, {\"start\": 22.84, \"end\": 31.18, \"text\": \"Today the tax reform bill passed the House 224-201.\"}, {\"start\": 31.18, \"end\": 37.86, \"text\": \"No Democrats backed it and a dozen Republicans voted no.\"}, {\"start\": 37.86, \"end\": 46.16, \"text\": \"It's the first major rewriting of U-S tax code in more than 30 years.\"}, {\"start\": 46.16, \"end\": 52.48, \"text\": \"Trump said at the heart of this bill is a tremendous amount of relief for the middle\"}, {\"start\": 52.48, \"end\": 61.54, \"text\": \"class -- including a doubling of the child tax credit and a nearly doubling of the standard\"}, {\"start\": 61.58, \"end\": 63.86, \"text\": \"deduction.\"}, {\"start\": 63.86, \"end\": 68.98, \"text\": \"He says Americans should start seeing the results in February.\"}, {\"start\": 68.98, \"end\": 73.98, \"text\": \"The measure now heads to President's Trump's desk for his signature.\"}, {\"start\": 75.14, \"end\": 79.12, \"text\": \"Republican leaders can't celebrate for too long.\"}, {\"start\": 79.12, \"end\": 85.12, \"text\": \"Congress faces a Friday deadline to keep the federal government funded and running.\"}, {\"start\": 85.12, \"end\": 90.52, \"text\": \"Democrats say if there is a shutdown the blame would fall squarely on Republicans because\"}, {\"start\": 90.54, \"end\": 95.66, \"text\": \"they have the majority of votes in the House and the Senate.\"}, {\"start\": 95.66, \"end\": 100.68, \"text\": \"One major sticking point among House and Senate Republicans appears to be\"}, {\"start\": 100.68, \"end\": 106.34, \"text\": \"Obamacare subsidy payments.\"}, {\"start\": 106.36, \"end\": 119.22, \"text\": \"These are payments made to insurance companies to lower deductibles and out-of-pocket costs\"}, {\"start\": 119.22, \"end\": 123.32, \"text\": \"to lower income Americans.\"}, {\"start\": 123.32, \"end\": 129.24, \"text\": \"On Wednesday some Republicans said they would drop a push for those payments to be included\"}, {\"start\": 129.32, \"end\": 132.34, \"text\": \"in a short-term spending bill, if it means avoiding a shutdown.\"}, {\"start\": 132.34, \"end\": 146.8, \"text\": \"Other thorny areas include a proposed $81 billion in disaster relief and defense spending.\"}, {\"start\": 146.8, \"end\": 151.88, \"text\": \"Not every Republican is keen on another short-term extension.\"}, {\"start\": 151.88, \"end\": 156.62, \"text\": \"But with time tight, some debates may have to be pushed into January if Congress wants\"}, {\"start\": 156.62, \"end\": 158.86, \"text\": \"to head home for the holidays.\"}, {\"start\": 161.72, \"end\": 167.34, \"text\": \"We want to warn you: some of the images in this story are disturbing.\"}, {\"start\": 167.34, \"end\": 177.76, \"text\": \"London's Metropolitan police worn acid attacks have increased by 74% this year.\"}, {\"start\": 177.76, \"end\": 182.08, \"text\": \"There's also been a notable increase nationwide.\"}, {\"start\": 182.08, \"end\": 190.3, \"text\": \"In England and Wales, there were 400 reported incidents in six months.\"}, {\"start\": 190.3, \"end\": 199.56, \"text\": \"In just one evening in July, there were five attacks on food delivery drivers in order\"}, {\"start\": 199.56, \"end\": 204.3, \"text\": \"to steal their mopeds.\"}, {\"start\": 204.3, \"end\": 209.18, \"text\": \"The attackers are mainly teenage boys and men.\"}, {\"start\": 209.2, \"end\": 218.08, \"text\": \"They are using chemicals that easy to find and cheap to buy at corner stores --\"}, {\"start\": 218.08, \"end\": 226.56, \"text\": \"corrosive substances like alkalis, ammonia and bleach.\"}, {\"start\": 226.88, \"end\": 237.96, \"text\": \"The range of crimes include moped robberies, gang violence, revenge and\"}, {\"start\": 237.96, \"end\": 243.0, \"text\": \"just random attacks.\"}, {\"start\": 243.0, \"end\": 249.52, \"text\": \"Public cries for government intervention are growing.\"}, {\"start\": 249.52, \"end\": 258.36, \"text\": \"Delivery drivers, who are one of the most targeted groups, want protection.\"}, {\"start\": 258.36, \"end\": 263.03, \"text\": \"The British government is reviewing how to impose strict restrictions on buying corrosive\"}, {\"start\": 263.04, \"end\": 267.24, \"text\": \"substances, although it admits that will be difficult.\"}, {\"start\": 267.3, \"end\": 273.06, \"text\": \"And it is considering stricter prison terms for offenders.\"}, {\"start\": 275.2, \"end\": 280.24, \"text\": \"Florida police officer John Cusack was hospitalized after being dragged by a speeding vehicle\"}, {\"start\": 280.24, \"end\": 282.78, \"text\": \"for about a half mile.\"}, {\"start\": 282.78, \"end\": 289.42, \"text\": \"On Tuesday Cusack was investigating a drug-related incident in a car.\"}, {\"start\": 289.42, \"end\": 297.9, \"text\": \"When he reached inside, the driver hit the gas pedal as Cusack held on for his life before\"}, {\"start\": 297.9, \"end\": 299.98, \"text\": \"letting go and tumbling dozens of times.\"}, {\"start\": 300.0, \"end\": 302.96, \"text\": \"And the entire incident was captured on his body camera.\"}, {\"start\": 303.0, \"end\": 305.08, \"text\": \"We have the dramatic video. Take a look...\"}, {\"start\": 334.24, \"end\": 342.74, \"text\": \"Authorities say Cusack has significant road rash injuries on his arms and legs but is\"}, {\"start\": 342.74, \"end\": 345.42, \"text\": \"expected to make a full recovery.\"}, {\"start\": 345.42, \"end\": 354.18, \"text\": \"After Cusack let go, the driver led police on a 20-mile chase.\"}, {\"start\": 354.18, \"end\": 360.56, \"text\": \"He was eventually caught and confessed that he took cocaine and heroin shortly before\"}, {\"start\": 360.56, \"end\": 362.86, \"text\": \"the incident occurred.\"}, {\"start\": 362.92, \"end\": 369.02, \"text\": \"The driver is now facing attempted murder charges.\"}, {\"start\": 370.98, \"end\": 376.02, \"text\": \"The U-S Coast Guard rescued a large sea turtle who was caught in numerous\"}, {\"start\": 376.1, \"end\": 379.9, \"text\": \"bales of confiscated cocaine.\"}, {\"start\": 379.9, \"end\": 385.14, \"text\": \"This happened during a 68-day drug patrol in the eastern Pacific.\"}, {\"start\": 385.14, \"end\": 399.12, \"text\": \"It's all part of \\\"Operation Martillo\\\", an international operation that includes 18 countries.\"}, {\"start\": 399.12, \"end\": 410.46, \"text\": \"Officials say close to 7 tons of cocaine and some marijuana were found.\"}, {\"start\": 410.46, \"end\": 416.18, \"text\": \"Two dozen alleged smugglers were taken into custody.\"}, {\"start\": 416.18, \"end\": 423.22, \"text\": \"And after carefully cutting twisted lines, the turtle was successfully free.\"}, {\"start\": 426.24, \"end\": 440.98, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga now has a residency engagement at the MGM Park theater in Las Vegas.\"}, {\"start\": 441.02, \"end\": 446.78, \"text\": \"The deal was signed over the weekend and the pop star will begin performing next year.\"}, {\"start\": 446.78, \"end\": 456.26, \"text\": \"She will perform 74 days with the possibility of adding more.\"}, {\"start\": 456.26, \"end\": 461.5, \"text\": \"The deal could be worth nearly $100 million.\"}, {\"start\": 461.52, \"end\": 470.14, \"text\": \"According to the Hollywood Reporter, Gaga will get upwards of $1 million per show.\"}, {\"start\": 470.14, \"end\": 479.56, \"text\": \"According to Pollstar, Lady Gaga grossed about $2.5 million per show on her last tour,\"}, {\"start\": 479.56, \"end\": 482.98, \"text\": \"which included 37 dates.\"}, {\"start\": 484.34, \"end\": 490.9, \"text\": \"Last month engineers blasted the Georgia Dome.\"}, {\"start\": 490.94, \"end\": 492.92, \"text\": \"But when the dust cleared two large walls\"}, {\"start\": 492.92, \"end\": 495.04, \"text\": \"still stood.\"}, {\"start\": 495.14, \"end\": 500.24, \"text\": \"What was left of the Georgia Dome came down with a big bang early Wednesday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 500.24, \"end\": 500.8, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 500.8, \"end\": 504.22, \"text\": \"3-2-1...\"}, {\"start\": 519.26, \"end\": 527.64, \"text\": \"Not only did the implosion make a massive dust cloud, it shook the ground and made quite\"}, {\"start\": 527.64, \"end\": 529.5, \"text\": \"a noise.\"}, {\"start\": 529.52, \"end\": 534.32, \"text\": \"Officials said if they had waited to do it during the day, all of the dust would have\"}, {\"start\": 534.32, \"end\": 536.9, \"text\": \"caused traffic problems.\"}, {\"start\": 536.9, \"end\": 541.7, \"text\": \"Crews will now start a major cleanup job.\"}, {\"start\": 543.0, \"end\": 544.8, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 544.8, \"end\": 546.0, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 546.0, \"end\": 547.8, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 547.8, \"end\": 551.36, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 551.46, \"end\": 556.92, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "0xYA1GwMQcE": {
    "video_id": "0xYA1GwMQcE",
    "title": "A healthier holiday (12.22.17)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171223",
    "duration": 61,
    "view_count": 223,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.9, \"end\": 9.58, \"text\": \"If you're looking to kickstart a healthier lifestyle, there's no better time than now.\"}, {\"start\": 9.58, \"end\": 15.32, \"text\": \"Here are some tips to help you celebrate a healthy holiday season.\"}, {\"start\": 15.32, \"end\": 22.12, \"text\": \"Go easy on the booze during the holidays.\"}, {\"start\": 22.12, \"end\": 29.78, \"text\": \"Alcohol temporarily keeps your body from burning fat.\"}, {\"start\": 29.78, \"end\": 37.5, \"text\": \"And additional sugar from the alcohol can cause your blood sugar to skyrocket.\"}, {\"start\": 37.5, \"end\": 43.4, \"text\": \"With all of the extra days off from work and school, don't just sit around all day.\"}, {\"start\": 43.4, \"end\": 45.56, \"text\": \"Stay active.\"}, {\"start\": 45.56, \"end\": 50.38, \"text\": \"Also try not to stress out too much.\"}, {\"start\": 50.38, \"end\": 55.1, \"text\": \"And don't skip sleep.\"}, {\"start\": 55.1, \"end\": 58.28, \"text\": \"The holiday season only comes around once a year.\"}, {\"start\": 58.28, \"end\": 60.0, \"text\": \"So enjoy it.\"}]"
  },
  "_zA4_EFlFZ4": {
    "video_id": "_zA4_EFlFZ4",
    "title": "How does the new tax bill affect you? (ASL - Sign1News - 12.16.17)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171217",
    "duration": 64,
    "view_count": 128,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.44, \"end\": 6.76, \"text\": \"Yesterday Republicans released the final version of their tax bill,\"}, {\"start\": 6.8, \"end\": 13.64, \"text\": \"which means they are one step closer to fulfilling the promise of passing tax breaks by Christmas.\"}, {\"start\": 13.64, \"end\": 19.34, \"text\": \"But how will the new tax bill affect you -- the taxpayer?\"}, {\"start\": 19.34, \"end\": 28.44, \"text\": \"You will see some benefits like a doubling of the standard deduction --\"}, {\"start\": 28.5, \"end\": 33.16, \"text\": \"although that's scheduled to go away after eight years.\"}, {\"start\": 33.16, \"end\": 39.0, \"text\": \"Your personal income tax rate may also lower by one or two percent\"}, {\"start\": 39.0, \"end\": 42.24, \"text\": \"depending on how much you make.\"}, {\"start\": 42.24, \"end\": 50.08, \"text\": \"If you have kids, that child tax credit doubles to $2,000.\"}, {\"start\": 50.08, \"end\": 57.74, \"text\": \"If that credit is more than what you owe in taxes, you get to keep most of that extra money.\"}, {\"start\": 57.74, \"end\": 63.3, \"text\": \"The new bill is scheduled to be presented for a vote on the House floor next week.\"}]"
  },
  "XF-FFbeyMJY": {
    "video_id": "XF-FFbeyMJY",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.14.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171215",
    "duration": 512,
    "view_count": 500,
    "description": "December 14, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-FCC VOTES TO END NET NEUTRALITY\n-NET NEUTRALITY PROTESTS\n-ROY MOORE STILL NOT CONCEDING THE ELECTION\n-LAWMAKER SAYS CLOTHING AN INVITATION TO HARASSMENT\n-WORKERS USE FORKLIFTS TO FOIL ROBBERY\n-HOW BIG WILL \"LAST JEDI\" OPEN?\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE Our talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAU",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.88, \"end\": 10.24, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.28, \"end\": 11.32, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.34, \"end\": 13.48, \"text\": \"Here a your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.72, \"end\": 23.08, \"text\": \"Today the Federal Communications Commission voted to repeal the net neutrality rule prohibiting\"}, {\"start\": 23.16, \"end\": 36.64, \"text\": \"internet security providers from prioritizing online content.\"}, {\"start\": 36.76, \"end\": 48.16, \"text\": \"So what in the world is net neutrality and why are people so passionate about it?\"}, {\"start\": 48.28, \"end\": 50.04, \"text\": \"Here's the explanation:\"}, {\"start\": 50.08, \"end\": 52.64, \"text\": \"The \\\"net\\\" refers to the Internet.\"}, {\"start\": 52.76, \"end\": 57.12, \"text\": \"The \\\"neutrality\\\" part is about keeping the Internet as it is today.\"}, {\"start\": 57.24, \"end\": 63.88, \"text\": \"It is a set of rules that went into effect in 2015 to prevent speed traps on the Internet.\"}, {\"start\": 63.88, \"end\": 72.24, \"text\": \"In other words speeding up access to some sites, slowing down access to others or\"}, {\"start\": 72.32, \"end\": 76.0, \"text\": \"blocking certain sites entirely.\"}, {\"start\": 76.24, \"end\": 89.28, \"text\": \"The companies that deliver your Internet like Comcast, Verizon and AT&amp;T have spent millions\"}, {\"start\": 89.68, \"end\": 93.04, \"text\": \"to get rid of net neutrality.\"}, {\"start\": 93.2, \"end\": 98.18, \"text\": \"They argue that having the government micromanage the business\"}, {\"start\": 98.22, \"end\": 103.52, \"text\": \"is not good for them or their consumers.\"}, {\"start\": 103.62, \"end\": 111.5, \"text\": \"On the other side are Internet giants like Facebook and Google,\"}, {\"start\": 111.58, \"end\": 118.56, \"text\": \"streaming services like Netflix and President Obama.\"}, {\"start\": 118.62, \"end\": 125.82, \"text\": \"They all argue the Internet is a public good and should be regulated like one.\"}, {\"start\": 125.84, \"end\": 134.56, \"text\": \"They also say the companies that own Internet pipelines could play favorites.\"}, {\"start\": 134.56, \"end\": 139.5, \"text\": \"For example a content provider like Netflix is in direct competition with Comcast, which\"}, {\"start\": 139.5, \"end\": 151.64, \"text\": \"owns NBC Universal and controls access to the Internet for over 20 million customers.\"}, {\"start\": 151.72, \"end\": 156.42, \"text\": \"You can imagine a scenario where NBC would want to speed up streams to its shows\"}, {\"start\": 156.48, \"end\": 160.28, \"text\": \"and slowdown streams to its rival Netflix.\"}, {\"start\": 160.28, \"end\": 166.02, \"text\": \"But Netflix can afford to pay for fast Internet service.\"}, {\"start\": 166.08, \"end\": 169.58, \"text\": \"It's worth more than $70 billion.\"}, {\"start\": 169.62, \"end\": 174.44, \"text\": \"The tiny startup company cannot.\"}, {\"start\": 176.08, \"end\": 182.2, \"text\": \"Today's vote led to many protests across the country.\"}, {\"start\": 182.28, \"end\": 188.58, \"text\": \"This was a vote closely watched by tech companies and Internet service providers.\"}, {\"start\": 188.6, \"end\": 198.64, \"text\": \"Many are concerned that repealing net neutrality will hurt consumers and small businesses.\"}, {\"start\": 198.72, \"end\": 204.64, \"text\": \"And it already looks like the FCC's decision is not likely to be the final word.\"}, {\"start\": 204.64, \"end\": 209.9, \"text\": \"Some in the technology industry have already indicated they are looking to see what legal\"}, {\"start\": 209.9, \"end\": 212.2, \"text\": \"options they have to challenge the vote.\"}, {\"start\": 213.56, \"end\": 224.38, \"text\": \"Two days after the shocking results of the Alabama Senate race, Republican Roy Moore is\"}, {\"start\": 224.38, \"end\": 229.56, \"text\": \"still not conceding the election to Democratic winner Doug Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 229.64, \"end\": 241.44, \"text\": \"Today Moore released a video on YouTube saying the \\\"political process has been influenced\"}, {\"start\": 241.44, \"end\": 248.96, \"text\": \"by baseless and false allegations\\\" -- meaning allegation related to his alleged sexual misconduct.\"}, {\"start\": 248.96, \"end\": 262.08, \"text\": \"And he says because military and provisional votes have not been counted yet, his campaign\"}, {\"start\": 262.24, \"end\": 267.12, \"text\": \"is still waiting for the election to be certified by the Alabama Secretary of State.\"}, {\"start\": 268.56, \"end\": 278.24, \"text\": \"House representative Marcy Kaptur from Ohio made shocking comments yesterday during the\"}, {\"start\": 278.64, \"end\": 282.88, \"text\": \"House Democratic meeting.\"}, {\"start\": 283.04, \"end\": 293.04, \"text\": \"She said women in Congress invite sexual harassment with the revealing clothing they wear.\"}, {\"start\": 293.36, \"end\": 303.12, \"text\": \"Kaptur told fellow lawmakers that quote \\\"too many members dressed inappropriately.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 303.12, \"end\": 311.76, \"text\": \"She added that female staffers and reporters are guilty of wearing revealing clothes.\"}, {\"start\": 311.76, \"end\": 320.64, \"text\": \"One Democrat at the meeting told CNN that many in the room were surprised by her comments.\"}, {\"start\": 320.64, \"end\": 328.05, \"text\": \"Kaptur later issued a statement saying she was not suggesting that victims are responsible\"}, {\"start\": 328.08, \"end\": 334.88, \"text\": \"and wanted to quote \\\"elevate the dress code to protect women from what is a pervasive\"}, {\"start\": 335.12, \"end\": 339.04, \"text\": \"problem here and in society at large.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 340.32, \"end\": 348.48, \"text\": \"Warehouse workers became heroes after foiling a brazen daytime robbery attempt.\"}, {\"start\": 348.48, \"end\": 355.52, \"text\": \"It happened in the Czech Republic and was caught on camera.\"}, {\"start\": 356.16, \"end\": 360.08, \"text\": \"The video shows the suspects pull a\"}, {\"start\": 360.08, \"end\": 362.56, \"text\": \"red vehicle up next to a construction van.\"}, {\"start\": 362.88, \"end\": 372.8, \"text\": \"After the suspects attempt to steal tools from the van, a scuffle ensues.\"}, {\"start\": 372.8, \"end\": 379.52, \"text\": \"When the suspects try to flee, the construction workers jump on nearby forklifts,\"}, {\"start\": 380.16, \"end\": 384.0, \"text\": \"blocking the vehicles escape route and trapping the suspects.\"}, {\"start\": 384.64, \"end\": 386.56, \"text\": \"We have the video. Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 409.6, \"end\": 414.08, \"text\": \"The suspects were later arrested by police.\"}, {\"start\": 414.08, \"end\": 423.84, \"text\": \"A spokesperson says the company released a video to highlight the worker's heroic efforts.\"}, {\"start\": 424.0, \"end\": 428.96, \"text\": \"It's already racked up over 200,000 views in less than a week.\"}, {\"start\": 429.76, \"end\": 431.62, \"text\": \"It's finally here!\"}, {\"start\": 431.68, \"end\": 438.4, \"text\": \"\\\"Star Wars: The Last Jedi\\\" opens this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 438.72, \"end\": 444.0, \"text\": \"And yes...\\\"the force\\\" will be strong.\"}, {\"start\": 444.16, \"end\": 449.44, \"text\": \"It's no doubt the movie will lead the weekend box office.\"}, {\"start\": 449.44, \"end\": 454.8, \"text\": \"The only question is how big its debut will be?\"}, {\"start\": 454.8, \"end\": 462.56, \"text\": \"Analysts expect episode eight in the movie franchise to bring in roughly $200 million\"}, {\"start\": 462.72, \"end\": 470.4, \"text\": \"in North America -- which would be the top debut of the year -- but well below the\"}, {\"start\": 470.4, \"end\": 487.04, \"text\": \"$248 million \\\"The Force Awakens\\\" opened with two years ago.\"}, {\"start\": 488.32, \"end\": 490.56, \"text\": \"And those your top stories.\"}, {\"start\": 490.56, \"end\": 491.86, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 491.9, \"end\": 493.88, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 494.24, \"end\": 497.86, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 497.88, \"end\": 503.52, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "DKEIfOqQMx4": {
    "video_id": "DKEIfOqQMx4",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.17.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180418",
    "duration": 427,
    "view_count": 1758,
    "description": "4.17.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-New ruling on immigration deportations\n-Southwest flight makes emergency landing in Philadelphia\n-Starbucks closing stores for racial bias training\n-Facebook class action lawsuit\n-Two surfers attacked by sharks in Australia\n-Rapper Kendrick Lamar wins a Pulitzer\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.42, \"end\": 10.32, \"text\": \"Hello everyone! Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.32, \"end\": 12.28, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.28, \"end\": 15.24, \"text\": \"Here are the top important stories of the day.\"}, {\"start\": 18.2, \"end\": 28.0, \"text\": \"The Supreme Court invalidated a federal statute requiring the deportation of immigrants\"}, {\"start\": 28.0, \"end\": 29.84, \"text\": \"convicted of some \\\"crimes of violence.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 30.84, \"end\": 43.6, \"text\": \"In the case, \\\"Sessions versus Dimaya,\\\" the court ruled that the provision was unconstitutionally\"}, {\"start\": 43.6, \"end\": 45.64, \"text\": \"vague.\"}, {\"start\": 45.64, \"end\": 53.84, \"text\": \"Observers were watching the case to get an idea of how the justices would handle President\"}, {\"start\": 53.84, \"end\": 63.28, \"text\": \"Trump's overall push to limit immigration and boost deportations.\"}, {\"start\": 63.28, \"end\": 82.04, \"text\": \"In the 5-4 ruling, Justice Neil Gorsuch voted to invalidate the statute.\"}, {\"start\": 82.04, \"end\": 97.8, \"text\": \"Gorsuch was confirmed last year to take the place of late justice Antonin Scalia.\"}, {\"start\": 97.8, \"end\": 103.16, \"text\": \"His decision in the case was in keeping with the jurisprudence of Scalia who also\"}, {\"start\": 103.16, \"end\": 111.96, \"text\": \"sided with the liberal wing of the court on vague statues and criminal convictions.\"}, {\"start\": 113.68, \"end\": 121.24, \"text\": \"A Southwest Airlines plane flying from New York to Dallas had to make an emergency landing\"}, {\"start\": 121.24, \"end\": 122.28, \"text\": \"in Philadelphia.\"}, {\"start\": 122.28, \"end\": 125.08, \"text\": \"When aircraft lost one of it's engines.\"}, {\"start\": 125.08, \"end\": 126.88, \"text\": \"The flight left LaGuardia heading to Dallas when the left engine stopped working.\"}, {\"start\": 126.96, \"end\": 137.44, \"text\": \"Shrapnel hit the window and caused serious injury.\"}, {\"start\": 137.44, \"end\": 146.24, \"text\": \"Several medical personnel on the flight tended to the injured passenger.\"}, {\"start\": 146.24, \"end\": 150.0, \"text\": \"The passenger was taken to the hospital where they later died.\"}, {\"start\": 150.0, \"end\": 156.8, \"text\": \"Authorities say a fuel leak caused the engine fire.\"}, {\"start\": 158.48, \"end\": 168.88, \"text\": \"Starbucks is closing its 8,000 company-owned stores in the U.S. on Tuesday, May 29 to educate\"}, {\"start\": 168.88, \"end\": 173.28, \"text\": \"employees on racial bias.\"}, {\"start\": 173.28, \"end\": 180.08, \"text\": \"The news follows an uproar over the arrest of two black men who were waiting for a friend\"}, {\"start\": 180.08, \"end\": 182.64, \"text\": \"at a Philadelphia Starbucks last week.\"}, {\"start\": 182.64, \"end\": 191.84, \"text\": \"The store manager called the police and the men were arrested for trespassing.\"}, {\"start\": 191.84, \"end\": 202.4, \"text\": \"The company says CEO Kevin Johnson met with the two on Monday and apologized for how they\"}, {\"start\": 202.48, \"end\": 205.6, \"text\": \"were treated.\"}, {\"start\": 205.92, \"end\": 212.96, \"text\": \"The racial bias training will be given to about 175,000 workers.\"}, {\"start\": 214.32, \"end\": 216.88, \"text\": \"Facebook is in more trouble.\"}, {\"start\": 216.88, \"end\": 222.3, \"text\": \"It comes after the recent revelation that a data firm tied to the Trump campaign improperly accessed\"}, {\"start\": 222.32, \"end\": 229.78, \"text\": \"user data in a voter targeting operation.\"}, {\"start\": 229.78, \"end\": 237.68, \"text\": \"This time it is a lawsuit for facial recognition software that scans user photos and suggests\"}, {\"start\": 237.68, \"end\": 240.54, \"text\": \"tagging friends.\"}, {\"start\": 240.54, \"end\": 246.54, \"text\": \"The plaintiffs are a group of Facebook users in Illinois.\"}, {\"start\": 246.7, \"end\": 250.54, \"text\": \"They say Facebook collects and stores users biometric data as a part of a face template\"}, {\"start\": 250.56, \"end\": 255.66, \"text\": \"without prior notice or consent.\"}, {\"start\": 255.86, \"end\": 264.72, \"text\": \"The US district ruled that claims are substantial enough to move forward in court.\"}, {\"start\": 264.72, \"end\": 269.2, \"text\": \"A Facebook spokesperson said the case has no merit and the company is reviewing the ruling.\"}, {\"start\": 269.2, \"end\": 275.12, \"text\": \"It's the latest blow to the company amid growing concerns about privacy.\"}, {\"start\": 276.8, \"end\": 285.08, \"text\": \"A shark attack on a surfer in Western Australia has forced the temporary suspension of an\"}, {\"start\": 285.08, \"end\": 288.4, \"text\": \"international surfing competition.\"}, {\"start\": 288.4, \"end\": 293.36, \"text\": \"The man was attacked at a surf spot known as Cobblestones.\"}, {\"start\": 293.36, \"end\": 300.56, \"text\": \"The victim was bitten on the leg by a shark and managed to paddle back to shore where\"}, {\"start\": 300.56, \"end\": 304.24, \"text\": \"a rescue helicopter carried him to the hospital.\"}, {\"start\": 304.32, \"end\": 309.68, \"text\": \"No one is certain of what type of shark is responsible or how big it was but officials\"}, {\"start\": 309.68, \"end\": 319.44, \"text\": \"have now confirmed a shark spotted in the area earlier was a 4 meter great white.\"}, {\"start\": 319.44, \"end\": 325.28, \"text\": \"Despite his injuries those who were there say the man remained conscious as he was given\"}, {\"start\": 325.28, \"end\": 327.6, \"text\": \"first aid by fellow surfers.\"}, {\"start\": 327.6, \"end\": 332.56, \"text\": \"Not long after the attack a second surfer was also attacked not far from where the first\"}, {\"start\": 332.56, \"end\": 334.0, \"text\": \"man was bitten.\"}, {\"start\": 334.0, \"end\": 335.76, \"text\": \"He has bite marks to his leg as well.\"}, {\"start\": 335.76, \"end\": 342.48, \"text\": \"15 people have now been killed by sharks off Western Australia since 2000.\"}, {\"start\": 343.28, \"end\": 355.84, \"text\": \"Kendrick Lamar won four Grammys this year for his album \\\"Damn.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 355.84, \"end\": 360.64, \"text\": \"Now he's won a Pulitzer!\"}, {\"start\": 360.64, \"end\": 374.08, \"text\": \"He's the first rapper ever to win the Pulitzer Prize for music which typically goes to classical\"}, {\"start\": 374.08, \"end\": 376.72, \"text\": \"or jazz artists.\"}, {\"start\": 376.72, \"end\": 385.04, \"text\": \"Lamar was praised for his politically charged performance at the Grammys in January.\"}, {\"start\": 385.12, \"end\": 396.56, \"text\": \"He also won Best Rap Performance, Best Rap Song, and Best Music Video for his song \\\"Humble.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 398.24, \"end\": 400.8, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for the day.\"}, {\"start\": 400.8, \"end\": 402.24, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 402.24, \"end\": 405.2, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 405.2, \"end\": 411.2, \"text\": \"And remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 411.2, \"end\": 414.24, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 414.24, \"end\": 416.16, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 416.16, \"end\": 420.8, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "hC-WIfOlVZg": {
    "video_id": "hC-WIfOlVZg",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.4.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180105",
    "duration": 579,
    "view_count": 1694,
    "description": "1.4.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-FALLOUT OVER BOMBSHELL BOOK ON WHITE HOUSE\n-WHITE HOUSE BANS PERSONAL CELL PHONES IN WEST WING\n-\"BOMB CYCLONE\" HAMMERING THE EAST COAST\n-MAJOR COMPUTER CHIP FLAW AFFECTS BILLIONS OF DEVICES\n-ABC STAGING \"SCANDAL\", \"MURDER\" CROSSOVER\n-AMAZON PATENTS \"SMART MIRROR\"\n-NO WINNER IN POWERBALL DRAWING\n-\"FUGITIVE FEUD\" TAKES AIM AT CROOKS\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 5.98, \"end\": 6.72, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 6.72, \"end\": 8.92, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.04, \"end\": 10.6, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 10.6, \"end\": 13.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 15.18, \"end\": 27.26, \"text\": \"The fallout over an upcoming book entitled \\\"Fire and Fury\\\" have White House officials\"}, {\"start\": 27.26, \"end\": 31.34, \"text\": \"scrambling, pointing fingers and threatening lawsuits.\"}, {\"start\": 31.34, \"end\": 34.18, \"text\": \"Excerpts with the book paint a picture of disorganization and constant infighting in\"}, {\"start\": 34.18, \"end\": 35.769, \"text\": \"the White House.\"}, {\"start\": 35.769, \"end\": 41.66, \"text\": \"And it calls into question President Trump's fitness to serve as Commander-in-Chief.\"}, {\"start\": 41.66, \"end\": 48.78, \"text\": \"A lawyer for President Trump has sent a cease-and-desist letter to the publisher of the book as well\"}, {\"start\": 48.78, \"end\": 64.96, \"text\": \"as to the president's former chief strategist Steve Bannon.\"}, {\"start\": 64.96, \"end\": 76.94, \"text\": \"In the book, Bannon says a 2016 meeting between Trump campaign officials and a Russian lawyer\"}, {\"start\": 76.94, \"end\": 83.34, \"text\": \"was \\\"treasonous.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 83.42, \"end\": 90.12, \"text\": \"But Bannon drew the president's fury after statements about the president's family appeared\"}, {\"start\": 90.12, \"end\": 91.62, \"text\": \"in the book.\"}, {\"start\": 91.7, \"end\": 98.14, \"text\": \"Bannon reportedly called Trump's daughter, Ivanka, \\\"dumb as a brick.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 98.14, \"end\": 107.26, \"text\": \"And he said Trump's son, Donald Trump Junior, would \\\"crack like an egg on national TV.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 107.26, \"end\": 113.95, \"text\": \"He was referring to Special Counsel Robert Mueller's investigation into Russia's tampering\"}, {\"start\": 113.95, \"end\": 117.98, \"text\": \"with the 2016 election.\"}, {\"start\": 117.98, \"end\": 128.52, \"text\": \"When reporters asked Trump about Bannon on Thursday he dismissed the controversy.\"}, {\"start\": 128.52, \"end\": 134.28, \"text\": \"The book was scheduled to be released next Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 134.28, \"end\": 142.6, \"text\": \"But due to unprecedented demand for it, publishers have moved its release date to this Friday,\"}, {\"start\": 142.62, \"end\": 144.06, \"text\": \"January 5th.\"}, {\"start\": 146.56, \"end\": 154.66, \"text\": \"Starting next week there will be no more personal cell phone use in the West Wing.\"}, {\"start\": 154.66, \"end\": 159.42, \"text\": \"The ban affects both White House staff and visitors.\"}, {\"start\": 159.42, \"end\": 168.02, \"text\": \"Staff can still use government-issued devices to conduct business.\"}, {\"start\": 168.08, \"end\": 173.3, \"text\": \"When asked why the ban was put in place, White House officials said it was for national security\"}, {\"start\": 173.3, \"end\": 175.54, \"text\": \"reasons.\"}, {\"start\": 175.54, \"end\": 184.42, \"text\": \"But sources close to the White House say the ban is aimed at limiting leaks about the Trump\"}, {\"start\": 184.42, \"end\": 186.96, \"text\": \"administration to reporters.\"}, {\"start\": 189.26, \"end\": 199.14, \"text\": \"Every East Coast state from Maine to Florida is under some type of winter storm watch or\"}, {\"start\": 199.14, \"end\": 203.74, \"text\": \"warning.\"}, {\"start\": 203.74, \"end\": 211.14, \"text\": \"And meteorologists expect it to stay that way for the rest of the week.\"}, {\"start\": 211.14, \"end\": 218.92, \"text\": \"This weather pattern is called a \\\"bomb cyclone\\\" and forecasters say it isn't letting up anytime\"}, {\"start\": 218.92, \"end\": 220.8, \"text\": \"soon.\"}, {\"start\": 220.8, \"end\": 228.36, \"text\": \"The East Coast is being hit with freezing rain, sleet, snow, hurricane-force winds and\"}, {\"start\": 228.36, \"end\": 230.12, \"text\": \"some wintry mix combinations.\"}, {\"start\": 230.12, \"end\": 236.88, \"text\": \"At least 16 people have died this week due to severe weather.\"}, {\"start\": 236.88, \"end\": 247.6, \"text\": \"Across the region governors are urging people to stay inside and stay off the slick roads.\"}, {\"start\": 247.6, \"end\": 255.72, \"text\": \"Flights have been grounded, schools closed and grocery store shelves are empty.\"}, {\"start\": 255.76, \"end\": 262.2, \"text\": \"Unfortunately, for many states, the worst is still to come.\"}, {\"start\": 262.2, \"end\": 270.56, \"text\": \"By the end of this week, parts of the Northeast will be colder than Mars.\"}, {\"start\": 273.88, \"end\": 281.4, \"text\": \"We have a huge warning about the chips in your computers and smart phones.\"}, {\"start\": 281.4, \"end\": 286.36, \"text\": \"Researchers say two major flaws in those computer chips could leave billions of devices vulnerable\"}, {\"start\": 286.36, \"end\": 290.64, \"text\": \"to security issues.\"}, {\"start\": 290.64, \"end\": 300.24, \"text\": \"The flaws expose data whenever the device's processor brings it up.\"}, {\"start\": 300.36, \"end\": 306.08, \"text\": \"Processors are considered the \\\"brain\\\" of the computer.\"}, {\"start\": 306.44, \"end\": 312.64, \"text\": \"Researchers say almost every computing system is affected by these flaws and they can allow\"}, {\"start\": 312.64, \"end\": 321.88, \"text\": \"attackers to read sensitive data stored in the device's memory, such as passwords.\"}, {\"start\": 321.92, \"end\": 326.88, \"text\": \"US government officials say the chips need to be replaced to completely fix the problems.\"}, {\"start\": 329.28, \"end\": 346.72, \"text\": \"The ABC network confirms that its shows \\\"Scandal\\\" and \\\"How To Get Away With Murder\\\" will both\"}, {\"start\": 346.72, \"end\": 348.8, \"text\": \"feature crossover episodes this season.\"}, {\"start\": 348.8, \"end\": 361.36, \"text\": \"Actresses Viola Davis and Kerry Washington broke the news on their social media accounts.\"}, {\"start\": 361.4, \"end\": 366.12, \"text\": \"Davis shared a photo of her portraying \\\"How To Get Away With Murder\\\" character Annalise\"}, {\"start\": 366.12, \"end\": 370.88, \"text\": \"Keating on the White House set of \\\"Scandal.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 370.96, \"end\": 376.4, \"text\": \"Washington did the same thing, posting an image of herself as \\\"Scandal's\\\" Olivia Pope\"}, {\"start\": 376.4, \"end\": 381.24, \"text\": \"in a courthouse corridor from \\\"How To Get Away With Murder.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 381.24, \"end\": 384.68, \"text\": \"Both shows are debuting new episodes January 18th.\"}, {\"start\": 384.68, \"end\": 388.4, \"text\": \"There's no word on when the crossover episodes will air.\"}, {\"start\": 390.48, \"end\": 400.8, \"text\": \"On Tuesday tech giant Amazon was granted a patent for a mirror which could superimpose\"}, {\"start\": 400.84, \"end\": 404.84, \"text\": \"virtual clothing onto your reflection.\"}, {\"start\": 404.84, \"end\": 419.16, \"text\": \"The mirror would also be able to place you in a virtual scene like a beach or a restaurant\"}, {\"start\": 419.16, \"end\": 422.56, \"text\": \"to match an outfit with an occasion.\"}, {\"start\": 422.6, \"end\": 429.96, \"text\": \"According to the patent, the mirror would use a combination of mirrors, lights, projectors,\"}, {\"start\": 429.96, \"end\": 436.48, \"text\": \"displays and cameras to project the image of a certain setting onto the display.\"}, {\"start\": 436.48, \"end\": 442.64, \"text\": \"It's not clear whether the mirror is currently in development at Amazon but it does give\"}, {\"start\": 442.76, \"end\": 446.52, \"text\": \"us a hint at what the company is working on.\"}, {\"start\": 446.52, \"end\": 449.72, \"text\": \"Amazon declined to comment.\"}, {\"start\": 452.2, \"end\": 458.72, \"text\": \"We're still waiting for the next big Powerball winner.\"}, {\"start\": 458.72, \"end\": 465.96, \"text\": \"There was no grand prize winner in Wednesday's $460 million-plus drawing.\"}, {\"start\": 465.96, \"end\": 472.28, \"text\": \"But at least six tickets won secondary prizes of $1 million or more.\"}, {\"start\": 472.32, \"end\": 479.96, \"text\": \"Because there was no big winner, Saturday night's Powerball jackpot will be an estimated\"}, {\"start\": 479.96, \"end\": 482.52, \"text\": \"$550 million.\"}, {\"start\": 482.52, \"end\": 489.24, \"text\": \"The Mega Millions jackpot also has a huge drawing coming up on Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 489.32, \"end\": 492.08, \"text\": \"The estimated jackpot is $445 million.\"}, {\"start\": 492.08, \"end\": 497.32, \"text\": \"This week marks the first time both lottery games offered prizes of at least $400 million\"}, {\"start\": 497.32, \"end\": 499.96, \"text\": \"at the same time.\"}, {\"start\": 502.92, \"end\": 519.08, \"text\": \"A Colorado Police Department is using the format of \\\"Family Feud\\\" to list top suspects\"}, {\"start\": 519.12, \"end\": 522.52, \"text\": \"on the run from the law.\"}, {\"start\": 522.52, \"end\": 529.04, \"text\": \"It's called \\\"Fugitive Feud\\\" and it was created by the Durango Police Department.\"}, {\"start\": 529.04, \"end\": 541.28, \"text\": \"The department hopes this new spin on traditional \\\"wanted\\\" posters will garner more attention.\"}, {\"start\": 541.28, \"end\": 551.36, \"text\": \"They say community involvement and social media presence is crucial in catching criminals.\"}, {\"start\": 553.12, \"end\": 555.6, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 555.6, \"end\": 557.04, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 557.04, \"end\": 559.44, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 559.44, \"end\": 564.64, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 564.64, \"end\": 572.48, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "R0EFhH15P_4": {
    "video_id": "R0EFhH15P_4",
    "title": "Miami bridge collapse: six vehicles recovered (ASL - 3.18.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180319",
    "duration": 66,
    "view_count": 172,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 2.0, \"end\": 7.8, \"text\": \"In Florida recovery workers have pulled six vehicles from the rubble of the collapsed\"}, {\"start\": 7.8, \"end\": 10.36, \"text\": \"pedestrian bridge.\"}, {\"start\": 10.36, \"end\": 19.84, \"text\": \"Officials say two cars were pulled out today with one body in one car and two bodies in\"}, {\"start\": 19.84, \"end\": 21.46, \"text\": \"the other.\"}, {\"start\": 21.46, \"end\": 28.44, \"text\": \"At least two bodies and four cars remain buried in the rubble.\"}, {\"start\": 28.44, \"end\": 34.18, \"text\": \"Crews hope to finish search and recovery efforts this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 34.18, \"end\": 42.02, \"text\": \"Rescuers say they are bracing themselves to find more victims than initially suspected.\"}, {\"start\": 42.04, \"end\": 49.3, \"text\": \"And rescuers are not just removing the bodies; they are honoring the victims as well.\"}, {\"start\": 53.14, \"end\": 61.2, \"text\": \"Every time a body is removed, rescuers stop everything and stand in silence as the body\"}, {\"start\": 61.2, \"end\": 64.76, \"text\": \"is taken away.\"}]"
  },
  "dL-3v-3u7ws": {
    "video_id": "dL-3v-3u7ws",
    "title": "Trump furious over \"Do Not Congratulate\" leak (ASL - 3.21.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180322",
    "duration": 94,
    "view_count": 176,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.6, \"end\": 12.74, \"text\": \"Sources in Washington, DC say President Trump is furious about leaked information regarding\"}, {\"start\": 12.74, \"end\": 23.48, \"text\": \"advice he received before his Tuesday phone call with Russian President Vladimir Putin.\"}, {\"start\": 23.48, \"end\": 37.56, \"text\": \"The Washington Post was the first to report that Trump congratulated Putin on being reelected,\"}, {\"start\": 37.56, \"end\": 42.74, \"text\": \"which his advisers had warned him not to do.\"}, {\"start\": 42.74, \"end\": 50.52, \"text\": \"Sources say only a few people would've known about that warning and the leak reinforces\"}, {\"start\": 50.52, \"end\": 57.4, \"text\": \"Trump's idea that some staffers want to undermine him.\"}, {\"start\": 57.4, \"end\": 64.92, \"text\": \"Today Trump defended his congrats to Putin in this tweet.\"}, {\"start\": 65.12, \"end\": 73.52, \"text\": \"It says: \\\"I called President Putin of Russia to congratulate him on his election victory.\"}, {\"start\": 73.52, \"end\": 76.84, \"text\": \"In past, Obama called him also.\"}, {\"start\": 76.84, \"end\": 86.12, \"text\": \"The fake news media is crazed because they want me to excoriate him.\"}, {\"start\": 86.12, \"end\": 88.0, \"text\": \"They are wrong!\"}, {\"start\": 88.0, \"end\": 93.2, \"text\": \"Getting along with Russia (and others) is a good thing, not a bad thing.\\\"\"}]"
  },
  "4xngx-JjvC8": {
    "video_id": "4xngx-JjvC8",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.20.18 - News in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180120",
    "duration": 427,
    "view_count": 1171,
    "description": "1.20.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-How does the government shutdown affect you?\n-Healthy dogs found in California torture house\n-2nd Annual Women’s March\n-Delta has new requirements for service animals\n-Tom Petty autopsy reveals accidental drug overdose\n-Super blue blood moon visible on January 31st\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.1, \"end\": 7.22, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.22, \"end\": 9.44, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.44, \"end\": 11.18, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 11.18, \"end\": 14.24, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.52, \"end\": 20.56, \"text\": \"The US government is officially shut down.\"}, {\"start\": 20.56, \"end\": 26.78, \"text\": \"And it falls on the one-year anniversary of Trump's inauguration.\"}, {\"start\": 26.78, \"end\": 31.66, \"text\": \"If you're wondering how the shutdown affects you, here's a breakdown:\"}, {\"start\": 31.72, \"end\": 35.68, \"text\": \"Federal workers will be affected right away.\"}, {\"start\": 35.7, \"end\": 39.62, \"text\": \"During the shutdown, most federal agencies close.\"}, {\"start\": 39.62, \"end\": 44.62, \"text\": \"Hundreds of thousands of workers will be furloughed or take a leave without pay.\"}, {\"start\": 44.62, \"end\": 48.34, \"text\": \"But not all federal workers.\"}, {\"start\": 48.34, \"end\": 55.3, \"text\": \"Those deemed essential will still work: air-traffic controllers, law enforcement, national security\"}, {\"start\": 55.3, \"end\": 57.64, \"text\": \"and federal court staff.\"}, {\"start\": 57.64, \"end\": 62.46, \"text\": \"But they won't be paid until after the shutdown ends.\"}, {\"start\": 62.48, \"end\": 64.32, \"text\": \"And what about the US military?\"}, {\"start\": 64.32, \"end\": 68.96, \"text\": \"The good news is the troops have already been paid for January.\"}, {\"start\": 68.96, \"end\": 72.92, \"text\": \"But a prolonged shutdown would hurt them.\"}, {\"start\": 72.92, \"end\": 76.88, \"text\": \"You will still get your Social Security check.\"}, {\"start\": 76.88, \"end\": 79.36, \"text\": \"That program is mandatory.\"}, {\"start\": 79.36, \"end\": 83.48, \"text\": \"The post office will keep running so your mail will be delivered on time.\"}, {\"start\": 83.48, \"end\": 87.84, \"text\": \"You can also get a new passport, but move quickly.\"}, {\"start\": 88.0, \"end\": 93.52, \"text\": \"Funding will run out if the shutdown drags on.\"}, {\"start\": 93.52, \"end\": 103.4, \"text\": \"You're out of luck if you planned to vacation to a national park, a museum or a monument.\"}, {\"start\": 103.4, \"end\": 109.84, \"text\": \"Taxpayer-funded sites will be closed, but the Trump administration is looking for ways\"}, {\"start\": 109.84, \"end\": 112.96, \"text\": \"to keep limited access where possible.\"}, {\"start\": 112.96, \"end\": 117.28, \"text\": \"So who does get paid during the shutdown?\"}, {\"start\": 117.44, \"end\": 124.28, \"text\": \"Those who have \\\"constitutional duties\\\" like the president, Supreme Court and members of\"}, {\"start\": 124.28, \"end\": 127.56, \"text\": \"Congress.\"}, {\"start\": 129.92, \"end\": 143.44, \"text\": \"Officials in California were shocked to find two happy and healthy dogs in the house where\"}, {\"start\": 143.44, \"end\": 145.44, \"text\": \"13 children were tortured.\"}, {\"start\": 145.44, \"end\": 152.76, \"text\": \"The dogs are both one-year-old Maltese puppies, one black, one white.\"}, {\"start\": 152.76, \"end\": 159.24, \"text\": \"Police say the dogs were clearly well fed, while the 13 children were starved and taunted\"}, {\"start\": 159.24, \"end\": 161.76, \"text\": \"with food they were not allowed to eat.\"}, {\"start\": 161.76, \"end\": 165.2, \"text\": \"The children are recovering in two hospitals.\"}, {\"start\": 165.32, \"end\": 169.04, \"text\": \"The dogs have been put up for adoption.\"}, {\"start\": 171.52, \"end\": 177.2, \"text\": \"2018 is being called the \\\"Year of the Woman.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 177.2, \"end\": 182.48, \"text\": \"This weekend women's events are taking place across the US and overseas.\"}, {\"start\": 185.28, \"end\": 190.52, \"text\": \"Many events are focused on making sure women vote and get involved in civic and political\"}, {\"start\": 190.52, \"end\": 191.6, \"text\": \"roles.\"}, {\"start\": 191.6, \"end\": 202.4, \"text\": \"At the event in Washington, DC, marchers plan to descend upon the White House after holding\"}, {\"start\": 202.4, \"end\": 203.96, \"text\": \"a rally at the Lincoln Memorial.\"}, {\"start\": 203.96, \"end\": 213.16, \"text\": \"More than a dozen speakers, from activists to politicians, will address the crowd that's\"}, {\"start\": 213.16, \"end\": 216.88, \"text\": \"ready to focus its attention on this year's midterm elections.\"}, {\"start\": 219.28, \"end\": 230.64, \"text\": \"On Friday Delta announced that beginning March 1st, all passengers bringing service animals\"}, {\"start\": 230.64, \"end\": 233.6, \"text\": \"into the cabin will be required to provide documentation from a doctor or mental health\"}, {\"start\": 233.6, \"end\": 236.88, \"text\": \"professional.\"}, {\"start\": 236.88, \"end\": 243.88, \"text\": \"They will also need a signed letter stating the animal is trained to behave without a\"}, {\"start\": 243.88, \"end\": 245.72, \"text\": \"kennel.\"}, {\"start\": 245.76, \"end\": 251.4, \"text\": \"The airline says the decision was made after repeated incidents involving untrained animals\"}, {\"start\": 251.4, \"end\": 255.56, \"text\": \"biting passengers and relieving themselves on airplanes.\"}, {\"start\": 255.56, \"end\": 262.48, \"text\": \"Delta will also no longer accept exotic or unusual service animals.\"}, {\"start\": 262.6, \"end\": 274.04, \"text\": \"The airline says some customers have tried to pass off turkeys, sugar gliders, snakes\"}, {\"start\": 274.28, \"end\": 277.44, \"text\": \"and spiders as comfort pets.\"}, {\"start\": 277.44, \"end\": 284.24, \"text\": \"According to the airline, about 700 service animals fly on its planes each day.\"}, {\"start\": 285.84, \"end\": 298.16, \"text\": \"Back in October singer Tom Petty collapsed at his Malibu home and later died at UCLA\"}, {\"start\": 298.16, \"end\": 301.28, \"text\": \"Medical Center.\"}, {\"start\": 301.28, \"end\": 308.12, \"text\": \"On Friday Petty's family and a medical examiner revealed the 66-year-old died of an accidental\"}, {\"start\": 308.36, \"end\": 311.08, \"text\": \"drug overdose of seven different medications.\"}, {\"start\": 311.08, \"end\": 319.56, \"text\": \"The medical examiner says Petty had four types of opioids in his system, along with two sedatives\"}, {\"start\": 319.56, \"end\": 322.84, \"text\": \"and an antidepressant.\"}, {\"start\": 322.96, \"end\": 334.84, \"text\": \"One of the opioids was acetyl fentanyl, which is not approved for medical use in the US.\"}, {\"start\": 334.84, \"end\": 343.2, \"text\": \"Petty's family says he had been touring with a fractured hip.\"}, {\"start\": 343.2, \"end\": 348.16, \"text\": \"But on the day he died, the fracture became a full-blown break.\"}, {\"start\": 348.16, \"end\": 354.52, \"text\": \"Petty's family believes he overused the medication to deal with the unbearable pain.\"}, {\"start\": 356.8, \"end\": 361.48, \"text\": \"You've heard of super moons, blue moons and blood moons.\"}, {\"start\": 361.48, \"end\": 369.2, \"text\": \"A \\\"supermoon\\\" occurs when the full moon is close to earth and brighter than normal.\"}, {\"start\": 369.2, \"end\": 379.36, \"text\": \"A \\\"blood moon\\\" occurs when it takes on a reddish tint as it passes through Earth's shadow in\"}, {\"start\": 379.36, \"end\": 381.6, \"text\": \"a lunar eclipse.\"}, {\"start\": 381.6, \"end\": 385.12, \"text\": \"A \\\"blue moon\\\" has nothing to do with color.\"}, {\"start\": 385.12, \"end\": 389.2, \"text\": \"It simply refers to the very unusual occurrence of two full moons in a single month.\"}, {\"start\": 389.2, \"end\": 395.96, \"text\": \"Depending on where you are on January 31st, you'll be able to see all three in one:\"}, {\"start\": 395.96, \"end\": 400.04, \"text\": \"a super blue blood moon.\"}, {\"start\": 401.76, \"end\": 404.08, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 404.08, \"end\": 405.76, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 405.76, \"end\": 408.24, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 408.24, \"end\": 413.08, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 413.12, \"end\": 419.4, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "n3Wg2bArIkw": {
    "video_id": "n3Wg2bArIkw",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.21.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180322",
    "duration": 416,
    "view_count": 1146,
    "description": "3.21.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Texas serial bomber killed, more bombs may be in region\n-Trump furious over \"Do Not Congratulate\" leak \n-Zuckerberg breaks silence, addresses data scandal\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN, FOX, ABC, CBS, TBN (TRINITY BROADCAST NETWORK), ATLANTA JO",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.42, \"end\": 8.84, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.84, \"end\": 12.02, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.02, \"end\": 13.34, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.34, \"end\": 17.14, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.42, \"end\": 35.18, \"text\": \"Police in Texas say this man, 24-year-old Mark Anthony Conditt, is responsible for the\"}, {\"start\": 35.18, \"end\": 40.36, \"text\": \"package bombings that killed two people and injured five others this month.\"}, {\"start\": 40.36, \"end\": 49.38, \"text\": \"Police believe surveillance cameras caught Conditt dropping packages off at a FedEx facility\"}, {\"start\": 49.38, \"end\": 51.0, \"text\": \"on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 51.0, \"end\": 58.14, \"text\": \"When investigators analyzed the bombs they realize they all had something in common:\"}, {\"start\": 58.14, \"end\": 64.72, \"text\": \"they were being made from common household ingredients.\"}, {\"start\": 64.72, \"end\": 71.16, \"text\": \"So they hit the area stores and started scanning receipts.\"}, {\"start\": 71.16, \"end\": 82.46, \"text\": \"That's how they were able to track down Conditt to a hotel outside of Austin.\"}, {\"start\": 82.46, \"end\": 92.26, \"text\": \"Once Conditt realized he was surrounded, he jumped into his car and drove off.\"}, {\"start\": 92.28, \"end\": 100.72, \"text\": \"When the SWAT team started closing in on the highway, police say Conditt detonated a bomb\"}, {\"start\": 100.72, \"end\": 105.38, \"text\": \"inside his car and killed himself.\"}, {\"start\": 105.38, \"end\": 111.5, \"text\": \"Investigators searching Conditt's home say they found more homemade explosive devices.\"}, {\"start\": 111.5, \"end\": 122.4, \"text\": \"There hoping to uncover information that will shed some light on a motive for Conditt's actions.\"}, {\"start\": 122.4, \"end\": 131.34, \"text\": \"Although the suspect is dead, investigators warn the danger may still exist.\"}, {\"start\": 135.36, \"end\": 146.14, \"text\": \"Police don't know yet if Conditt had an accomplice and there is a possibility more bombs may\"}, {\"start\": 146.14, \"end\": 149.26, \"text\": \"still be in the area.\"}, {\"start\": 152.26, \"end\": 161.38, \"text\": \"Sources in Washington, DC say President Trump is furious about leaked information regarding\"}, {\"start\": 161.38, \"end\": 174.08, \"text\": \"advice he received before his Tuesday phone call with Russian President Vladimir Putin.\"}, {\"start\": 174.08, \"end\": 187.9, \"text\": \"The Washington Post was the first to report that Trump congratulated Putin on being reelected,\"}, {\"start\": 187.9, \"end\": 193.3, \"text\": \"which his advisers had warned him not to do.\"}, {\"start\": 193.3, \"end\": 201.24, \"text\": \"Sources say only a few people would've known about that warning and the leak reinforces\"}, {\"start\": 201.28, \"end\": 208.04, \"text\": \"Trump's idea that some staffers want to undermine him.\"}, {\"start\": 208.04, \"end\": 215.74, \"text\": \"Today Trump defended his congrats to Putin in this tweet.\"}, {\"start\": 215.74, \"end\": 224.4, \"text\": \"It says: \\\"I called President Putin of Russia to congratulate him on his election victory.\"}, {\"start\": 224.4, \"end\": 227.44, \"text\": \"In past, Obama called him also.\"}, {\"start\": 227.44, \"end\": 236.94, \"text\": \"The fake news media is crazed because they want me to excoriate him.\"}, {\"start\": 236.94, \"end\": 238.5, \"text\": \"They are wrong!\"}, {\"start\": 238.5, \"end\": 243.96, \"text\": \"Getting along with Russia (and others) is a good thing, not a bad thing.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 247.48, \"end\": 262.4, \"text\": \"For the first time, we are hearing from Facebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg about a data scandal engulfing\"}, {\"start\": 262.4, \"end\": 267.58, \"text\": \"the social media giant.\"}, {\"start\": 267.58, \"end\": 279.14, \"text\": \"He posted a comment on Facebook saying the company has a responsibility to protect user data.\"}, {\"start\": 279.14, \"end\": 285.9, \"text\": \"He says Facebook will take a series of steps to fix what he called a \\\"breach of trust\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 285.9, \"end\": 289.8, \"text\": \"between Facebook and its users.\"}, {\"start\": 289.8, \"end\": 299.0, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg also says he's working to understand what exactly happened.\"}, {\"start\": 299.0, \"end\": 310.2, \"text\": \"Also today a class-action lawsuit was filed in federal court against Facebook and Cambridge\"}, {\"start\": 310.2, \"end\": 322.26, \"text\": \"Analytica for collecting the personal information of 50 million Facebook users.\"}, {\"start\": 322.26, \"end\": 328.02, \"text\": \"It was filed by a Maryland woman who says her privacy was violated when her information\"}, {\"start\": 328.02, \"end\": 332.44, \"text\": \"was disclosed without permission.\"}, {\"start\": 332.44, \"end\": 344.32, \"text\": \"The lawsuit was filed in federal court in San Jose, California, where Facebook is based.\"}, {\"start\": 344.32, \"end\": 352.78, \"text\": \"The woman says the lawsuit is for all Facebook users in the US whose personal information\"}, {\"start\": 352.78, \"end\": 363.76, \"text\": \"was obtained by Cambridge Analytica without authorization.\"}, {\"start\": 363.76, \"end\": 369.98, \"text\": \"A judge will decide whether the lawsuit will be certified as a class action.\"}, {\"start\": 369.98, \"end\": 378.0, \"text\": \"If that happens and you think your personal information was collected, we will update\"}, {\"start\": 378.0, \"end\": 382.5, \"text\": \"you on how you can become part of the class action lawsuit.\"}, {\"start\": 386.38, \"end\": 390.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 390.02, \"end\": 391.56, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 391.56, \"end\": 394.74, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 394.74, \"end\": 400.66, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 400.66, \"end\": 407.26, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "jafgm6k2NYA": {
    "video_id": "jafgm6k2NYA",
    "title": "Sign1News 12.6.2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171207",
    "duration": 704,
    "view_count": 403,
    "description": "December 6, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-CALIFORNIA WILDFIRES UPDATE\n-TRUMP SIGNS RESOLUTION RECOGNIZING JERUSALEM\n-DOZENS OF SENATORS CALL FOR FRANKEN TO RESIGN\n-FREDDIE GRAY PROSECUTOR FACES LAWSUIT BY POLICE\n-NO ARREST FOR FAKE TAMPA INTERPRETER\n-\"TIME\" PERSON OF THE YEAR: THE SILENCE BREAKERS\n-LONGEST STANDING RAINBOW BREAKS RECORD\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality ne",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.32, \"end\": 9.16, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.16, \"end\": 10.04, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 10.24, \"end\": 13.2, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 13.64, \"end\": 18.56, \"text\": \"A dire situation is unfolding in Southern California.\"}, {\"start\": 18.64, \"end\": 25.64, \"text\": \"Tens of thousands of people have been forced to evacuate because of several raging wildfires.\"}, {\"start\": 25.64, \"end\": 38.12, \"text\": \"More than 83,000 acres have burned and officials say it will only get worse before it gets better.\"}, {\"start\": 38.2, \"end\": 44.84, \"text\": \"Part of Interstate 405 has been shut down because the fires are burning dangerously\"}, {\"start\": 44.96, \"end\": 47.88, \"text\": \"close to the road.\"}, {\"start\": 47.92, \"end\": 53.12, \"text\": \"Schools have been shut down and there has been widespread power outages.\"}, {\"start\": 53.16, \"end\": 62.72, \"text\": \"The largest wildfire is burning in Ventura County just northwest of Los Angeles.\"}, {\"start\": 62.8, \"end\": 69.52, \"text\": \"Governor Jerry Brown has declared a state of emergency.\"}, {\"start\": 69.68, \"end\": 74.48, \"text\": \"President Trump tweeted this:\"}, {\"start\": 74.64, \"end\": 80.04, \"text\": \"\\\"Our thoughts and prayers are with everyone in the path of the wildfires.\"}, {\"start\": 80.12, \"end\": 85.44, \"text\": \"I encourage everyone to heed the advice of officials.\"}, {\"start\": 85.52, \"end\": 92.2, \"text\": \"And thank you to all the first responders for your incredible work.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 94.2, \"end\": 102.64, \"text\": \"Today President Trump officially signed the resolution recognizing Jerusalem\"}, {\"start\": 102.68, \"end\": 107.56, \"text\": \"as Israel's capital.\"}, {\"start\": 107.68, \"end\": 115.36, \"text\": \"It was part of a campaign promise he made when he was running for president.\"}, {\"start\": 115.4, \"end\": 127.72, \"text\": \"Trump cited a law Congress actually passed in 1995 -- to move the U.S. Embassy from\"}, {\"start\": 127.84, \"end\": 140.4, \"text\": \"Tel Aviv to Jerusalem out of respect for Israel's recognition of the city as its capital.\"}, {\"start\": 140.56, \"end\": 151.08, \"text\": \"But since then Presidents Clinton, Bush and Obama all signed waivers every six months\"}, {\"start\": 151.16, \"end\": 171.76, \"text\": \"to halt the move, in the name of national security interests and the peace process.\"}, {\"start\": 171.84, \"end\": 180.52, \"text\": \"President Trump spoke with a number of leaders in the region on Tuesday and all of them are\"}, {\"start\": 180.64, \"end\": 191.08, \"text\": \"opposed to the move, expressing concern about stability in an already tense region.\"}, {\"start\": 191.08, \"end\": 200.48, \"text\": \"Palestinian protesters called for three days of rage.\"}, {\"start\": 200.48, \"end\": 209.84, \"text\": \"European allies have also asked the President to reconsider.\"}, {\"start\": 209.96, \"end\": 216.76, \"text\": \"And even Pope Francis expressed concern.\"}, {\"start\": 216.84, \"end\": 226.72, \"text\": \"They believe it could further complicate sensitive elements in peace negotiations.\"}, {\"start\": 226.8, \"end\": 229.68, \"text\": \"Trump disagrees.\"}, {\"start\": 229.76, \"end\": 239.96, \"text\": \"And so does Israeli prime minister Benjamin Netanyahu.\"}, {\"start\": 240.04, \"end\": 259.16, \"text\": \"He called the move an important step towards peace.\"}, {\"start\": 259.2, \"end\": 269.08, \"text\": \"The process of moving the U.S. Embassy could take years.\"}, {\"start\": 269.12, \"end\": 274.76, \"text\": \"No other countries have their embassies in Jerusalem,\"}, {\"start\": 274.76, \"end\": 282.36, \"text\": \"although the U.S. currently has a consulate there.\"}, {\"start\": 282.52, \"end\": 290.48, \"text\": \"Trump also said Vice President Mike Pence will visit the region in the coming days.\"}, {\"start\": 292.2, \"end\": 304.88, \"text\": \"Over a dozen Democratic senators have called on their colleague Al Franken to resign due to\"}, {\"start\": 304.96, \"end\": 309.64, \"text\": \"the sexual harassment allegations against him.\"}, {\"start\": 309.64, \"end\": 322.72, \"text\": \"The first Senator to call for Franken's resignation is New York's Kirsten Gillibrand.\"}, {\"start\": 322.76, \"end\": 331.84, \"text\": \"She wrote on Facebook that it would be better for the U.S. for Franken to step aside and\"}, {\"start\": 331.92, \"end\": 333.88, \"text\": \"let someone else serve.\"}, {\"start\": 333.88, \"end\": 344.16, \"text\": \"Gillibrand says Franken must send a clear message that any kind of mistreatment of women\"}, {\"start\": 344.2, \"end\": 346.96, \"text\": \"is not acceptable.\"}, {\"start\": 347.16, \"end\": 354.52, \"text\": \"Franken has said he has never intentionally engaged in such conduct and will cooperate\"}, {\"start\": 354.6, \"end\": 364.28, \"text\": \"with a Senate ethics committee investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 365.6, \"end\": 375.12, \"text\": \"A federal appeals court is being asked to decide whether Baltimore's prosecutor should\"}, {\"start\": 375.2, \"end\": 378.64, \"text\": \"face a lawsuit by five city police officers.\"}, {\"start\": 378.72, \"end\": 387.0, \"text\": \"The case involves the 2015 death of Freddie Gray, an African-American man who died in\"}, {\"start\": 387.08, \"end\": 390.36, \"text\": \"Baltimore police custody.\"}, {\"start\": 390.36, \"end\": 400.2, \"text\": \"His death sparked days of riots and protests against police brutality nationwide.\"}, {\"start\": 400.32, \"end\": 414.44, \"text\": \"Baltimore state's attorney Marilyn Mosby charged six officers in connection to Gray's death.\"}, {\"start\": 414.52, \"end\": 419.48, \"text\": \"Three of the officers were found not guilty on all counts\"}, {\"start\": 419.48, \"end\": 423.96, \"text\": \"and charges were dropped against the others.\"}, {\"start\": 424.16, \"end\": 434.44, \"text\": \"Five of those officers are now suing Mosby for malicious prosecution.\"}, {\"start\": 434.44, \"end\": 442.48, \"text\": \"But Mosby says she is immune from such lawsuits.\"}, {\"start\": 444.84, \"end\": 453.24, \"text\": \"The Deaf community is still talking about this woman.\"}, {\"start\": 453.24, \"end\": 457.0, \"text\": \"This image is courtesy of CNN.com.\"}, {\"start\": 457.08, \"end\": 461.84, \"text\": \"The woman's name is Derlyn Roberts.\"}, {\"start\": 461.88, \"end\": 469.12, \"text\": \"Police in Tampa say she showed up for a major press conference announcing the arrest of\"}, {\"start\": 469.12, \"end\": 476.76, \"text\": \"the Seminole Heights murder suspect.\"}, {\"start\": 476.84, \"end\": 482.32, \"text\": \"Roberts pretended to be an American sign language interpreter.\"}, {\"start\": 482.32, \"end\": 488.36, \"text\": \"But her signs were complete gibberish.\"}, {\"start\": 488.36, \"end\": 494.64, \"text\": \"To make matters worse, the mother of one of the victims is Deaf\"}, {\"start\": 494.68, \"end\": 498.8, \"text\": \"and she was at the press conference.\"}, {\"start\": 498.8, \"end\": 505.64, \"text\": \"Tampa police say they have contracted an interpreting agency in the past\"}, {\"start\": 505.72, \"end\": 516.72, \"text\": \"but admitted they did not properly question Roberts when she arrived.\"}, {\"start\": 516.88, \"end\": 528.2, \"text\": \"Police say they later learned Roberts had been arrested several times for fraud but\"}, {\"start\": 528.2, \"end\": 533.52, \"text\": \"she would not be arrested in this case.\"}, {\"start\": 533.52, \"end\": 540.96, \"text\": \"Police say she committed an ethical violation pretending to be an interpreter\"}, {\"start\": 541.0, \"end\": 544.88, \"text\": \"but that is not a crime.\"}, {\"start\": 547.24, \"end\": 561.36, \"text\": \"TIME magazine has named \\\"The Silence Breakers\\\" as the 2017 \\\"Person of the Year.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 561.44, \"end\": 567.36, \"text\": \"\\\"The Silence Breakers\\\" represent the women who triggered a #METOO\"}, {\"start\": 567.36, \"end\": 571.52, \"text\": \"national outcry over sexual harassment.\"}, {\"start\": 571.72, \"end\": 588.68, \"text\": \"The cover features actress Ashley Judd, singer Taylor Swift, former Uber engineer Susan Fowler,\"}, {\"start\": 588.76, \"end\": 600.84, \"text\": \"activist Tarana Burke who started the concept of #METOO, corporate lobbyist Adama Iwu,\"}, {\"start\": 601.0, \"end\": 612.88, \"text\": \"worker Isabel Pascual and a woman whose face is obscured.\"}, {\"start\": 612.92, \"end\": 622.88, \"text\": \"That face is intended to represent the women who haven't yet come forward.\"}, {\"start\": 622.88, \"end\": 632.76, \"text\": \"TIME's editor-in-chief said that the people who spoke out about harassment have created\"}, {\"start\": 632.84, \"end\": 638.72, \"text\": \"one of the largest shifts in our culture in decades.\"}, {\"start\": 642.56, \"end\": 650.56, \"text\": \"A low-hanging rainbow was on display over a city in Taiwan for nearly 9 hours.\"}, {\"start\": 650.6, \"end\": 661.28, \"text\": \"It was caught on camera by teachers and students at the Chinese Culture University in Taipei.\"}, {\"start\": 661.4, \"end\": 670.0, \"text\": \"It is now in the Guinness Book of World Records as the longest lasting rainbow.\"}, {\"start\": 670.12, \"end\": 679.56, \"text\": \"The previous record was six hours set in Yorkshire, England in 1994.\"}, {\"start\": 682.2, \"end\": 683.84, \"text\": \"And those your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 684.0, \"end\": 684.88, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 684.96, \"end\": 687.36, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 687.36, \"end\": 691.64, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 691.76, \"end\": 697.32, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "TXP1RMKwABE": {
    "video_id": "TXP1RMKwABE",
    "title": "Sign1News 4.28.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180428",
    "duration": 368,
    "view_count": 1006,
    "description": "4.28.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Judge puts a 90 daydelay on Stormy Daniel lawsuit\n-Bill Cosby is placed under house arrest\n-Ford will stop selling certain cars in the U.S.\n-Chance The Rapper rejects a 'Thank You' from the President\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY, CNN, FOX, ABC, CBS",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.24, \"end\": 9.18, \"text\": \"Hello everyone\"}, {\"start\": 9.18, \"end\": 10.84, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.84, \"end\": 12.44, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 12.44, \"end\": 15.78, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.28, \"end\": 29.12, \"text\": \"Stormy Daniels, the adult film star who said she had an affair with President Trump and\"}, {\"start\": 29.12, \"end\": 32.16, \"text\": \"is now suing him.\"}, {\"start\": 32.16, \"end\": 40.74, \"text\": \"Her lawsuit against the President and his personal attorney\"}, {\"start\": 40.86, \"end\": 47.9, \"text\": \"Michael Cohen is on hold.\"}, {\"start\": 47.9, \"end\": 54.51, \"text\": \"The judge in the case announced that there would be a 90 day delay.\"}, {\"start\": 54.51, \"end\": 60.88, \"text\": \"The delay was requested by Cohen himself.\"}, {\"start\": 60.88, \"end\": 68.68, \"text\": \"Cohen doesn't want to incriminate himself during the trial.\"}, {\"start\": 68.68, \"end\": 76.399, \"text\": \"He has to wait for the FBI investigation to finish first.\"}, {\"start\": 76.399, \"end\": 88.799, \"text\": \"Cohen paid Stormy $130,000 to remain silent about her affair with the President.\"}, {\"start\": 88.799, \"end\": 94.329, \"text\": \"Trump denies having the affair.\"}, {\"start\": 94.329, \"end\": 114.0, \"text\": \"However, the President acknowledged that Cohen did represent him in the Stormy Daniel case.\"}, {\"start\": 116.24, \"end\": 125.84, \"text\": \"Bill Cosby is under house arrest and he must wear a GPS monitor.\"}, {\"start\": 125.84, \"end\": 131.44, \"text\": \"But he will be allowed to travel to see his doctors and attorneys.\"}, {\"start\": 131.44, \"end\": 140.36, \"text\": \"Cosby was found guilty on three counts of aggravated indecent assault.\"}, {\"start\": 140.36, \"end\": 153.72, \"text\": \"Accuser Andrea Constand said he druggged and assaulted her at his home in 2004.\"}, {\"start\": 153.72, \"end\": 162.4, \"text\": \"Cosby's sentencing hearing has not been scheduled yet.\"}, {\"start\": 162.4, \"end\": 168.28, \"text\": \"Cosby could get up to 30 years in prison.\"}, {\"start\": 172.72, \"end\": 193.52, \"text\": \"The automaker Ford has decided to stop selling its Fiesta, Taurus, Fusion and Focus\"}, {\"start\": 193.52, \"end\": 197.84, \"text\": \"in the U.S.\"}, {\"start\": 197.96, \"end\": 207.4, \"text\": \"Ford officials say the only passenger car models that will stay in production are the\"}, {\"start\": 207.4, \"end\": 223.24, \"text\": \"Mustang and the upcoming Ford Focus Active, a hatchback-like a vehicle set to make his\"}, {\"start\": 223.24, \"end\": 225.68, \"text\": \"debut next year.\"}, {\"start\": 225.68, \"end\": 237.8, \"text\": \"Ford will, however, continue to sell his trucks, SUVs and crossovers.\"}, {\"start\": 241.92, \"end\": 254.28, \"text\": \"Chance The Rapper has rejected a thank you from President Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 254.28, \"end\": 266.12, \"text\": \"The President praised Kanye West for supporting him and he thanked Chance.\"}, {\"start\": 266.13, \"end\": 277.44, \"text\": \"But Chance tweeted back \\\"Nah, that ain't it, yo.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 277.44, \"end\": 282.71, \"text\": \"Why did the President thank Chance?\"}, {\"start\": 282.71, \"end\": 296.87, \"text\": \"Chance defended West by tweeting quote, \\\"Black people don't have to be Democrats\\\".\"}, {\"start\": 296.88, \"end\": 307.72, \"text\": \"That's tweet created backlash against Chance, but he explained on Twitter that his support\"}, {\"start\": 307.72, \"end\": 313.07, \"text\": \"was for West, not TrUmp.\"}, {\"start\": 313.08, \"end\": 325.68, \"text\": \"Also Chance was the first rapper to bring his own interpreter to a show.\"}, {\"start\": 325.68, \"end\": 335.0, \"text\": \"Other rappers have had interpreters provided by the venue.\"}, {\"start\": 338.2, \"end\": 340.76, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for the day.\"}, {\"start\": 340.76, \"end\": 343.08, \"text\": \"I am Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 343.08, \"end\": 345.96, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 345.96, \"end\": 351.88, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 351.88, \"end\": 354.76, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 354.76, \"end\": 356.48, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 356.48, \"end\": 360.32, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "GaVM8qXM9t0": {
    "video_id": "GaVM8qXM9t0",
    "title": "Waymo wants to prevent vomiting in self-driving cars (ASL - 2.24.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180224",
    "duration": 70,
    "view_count": 187,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.22, \"end\": 10.86, \"text\": \"Waymo, the company behind a self-driving car project, says it has the technology that will\"}, {\"start\": 10.86, \"end\": 16.46, \"text\": \"prevent motion sickness in its vehicles.\"}, {\"start\": 16.46, \"end\": 28.82, \"text\": \"The technology would choose routes without stop-and-go traffic to spare motion-sensitive\"}, {\"start\": 28.82, \"end\": 32.64, \"text\": \"passengers.\"}, {\"start\": 32.64, \"end\": 40.86, \"text\": \"It would also reduce sudden acceleration and back-and-forth swaying of the vehicle.\"}, {\"start\": 40.86, \"end\": 51.84, \"text\": \"On top of that, self-driving cars would tell sensitive passengers which seat to take to\"}, {\"start\": 51.84, \"end\": 53.92, \"text\": \"minimize motion sickness.\"}, {\"start\": 53.92, \"end\": 60.64, \"text\": \"Waymo is applying for a patent related to the new technology.\"}, {\"start\": 60.64, \"end\": 68.92, \"text\": \"The company plans to launch a public self-driving service in Arizona later this year.\"}]"
  },
  "wRp58NgrSo8": {
    "video_id": "wRp58NgrSo8",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.27.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180328",
    "duration": 502,
    "view_count": 999,
    "description": "3.27.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Police ask for calm in Stephon Clark protests\n-Mark Zuckerberg decides to testify before Congress\n-Heineken pulls \"Lighter\" ad after racism claims\n-Toddler fills in as prom date for Marine\n-How are you spending your tax refund?\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UN",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.58, \"end\": 8.96, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.96, \"end\": 11.16, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.16, \"end\": 12.6, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.6, \"end\": 15.56, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.42, \"end\": 29.46, \"text\": \"The police chief in Sacramento is asking protesters to exercise calm to prevent any more tragedies,\"}, {\"start\": 29.46, \"end\": 34.26, \"text\": \"injuries or property damage.\"}, {\"start\": 34.26, \"end\": 41.08, \"text\": \"The marchers are protesting the shooting death of Stephon Clark.\"}, {\"start\": 41.08, \"end\": 48.26, \"text\": \"Last week police fired 20 rounds at him while he was standing in his grandmother's backyard.\"}, {\"start\": 48.26, \"end\": 51.74, \"text\": \"He was struck multiple times and was pronounced dead at the scene.\"}, {\"start\": 51.74, \"end\": 56.4, \"text\": \"Police say they thought Clark was pointing a gun at them when in actuality he was only\"}, {\"start\": 56.46, \"end\": 58.38, \"text\": \"holding a cell phone.\"}, {\"start\": 58.38, \"end\": 64.52, \"text\": \"Because emotions are running extremely high in this case, Sacramento officials have asked\"}, {\"start\": 64.6, \"end\": 69.48, \"text\": \"the state's Attorney General to step in and conduct an independent investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 69.48, \"end\": 74.68, \"text\": \"Both police officers involved in the shooting have been placed on paid administrative leave.\"}, {\"start\": 74.68, \"end\": 79.4, \"text\": \"Their names have not been released.\"}, {\"start\": 79.56, \"end\": 89.16, \"text\": \"A GoFundMe account set up to help Clark's family with funeral expenses has already raised\"}, {\"start\": 89.16, \"end\": 91.94, \"text\": \"nearly $62,000.\"}, {\"start\": 95.56, \"end\": 110.12, \"text\": \"It appears Facebook CEO Mark Zuckerberg has succumbed to pressure from US lawmakers.\"}, {\"start\": 110.12, \"end\": 116.46, \"text\": \"He will now testify at a Senate hearing on April 10.\"}, {\"start\": 116.46, \"end\": 127.26, \"text\": \"This all comes after Cambridge Analytica reportedly accessed information from about 50 million\"}, {\"start\": 127.26, \"end\": 129.6, \"text\": \"Facebook users without their knowledge.\"}, {\"start\": 129.66, \"end\": 141.02, \"text\": \"Zuckerberg's willingness to testify means Google CEO Sundar Pinchai and twitter CEO\"}, {\"start\": 141.02, \"end\": 148.5, \"text\": \"Jack Dorsey could be next.\"}, {\"start\": 148.52, \"end\": 158.4, \"text\": \"Senate Judiciary Chairman Chuck Grassley officially invited all of them to the hearing.\"}, {\"start\": 158.4, \"end\": 165.68, \"text\": \"While Zuckerberg is willing to testify in the US, he has turned down a summons from\"}, {\"start\": 165.68, \"end\": 168.38, \"text\": \"UK lawmakers.\"}, {\"start\": 168.38, \"end\": 177.0, \"text\": \"Last week the British House of Commons asked Zuckerberg to fly to London and face questions\"}, {\"start\": 177.0, \"end\": 185.0, \"text\": \"about the way the social media giant handles private user data.\"}, {\"start\": 185.0, \"end\": 186.96, \"text\": \"He said no.\"}, {\"start\": 186.96, \"end\": 198.74, \"text\": \"Instead Facebook offered up the company's Chief Tech Officer and the Chief Product Officer.\"}, {\"start\": 200.62, \"end\": 212.66, \"text\": \"Beer maker Heineken is facing severe backlash for its latest commercial.\"}, {\"start\": 212.66, \"end\": 221.779, \"text\": \"It features a bartender sliding a bottle of Heineken Light to a woman.\"}, {\"start\": 221.779, \"end\": 229.329, \"text\": \"The bottle travels past several black people before arriving at the lighter skinned woman.\"}, {\"start\": 229.329, \"end\": 234.34, \"text\": \"The commercial ends with the tagline \\\"Sometimes lighter is better.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 234.34, \"end\": 236.94, \"text\": \"If you haven't seen the commercial, here it is.\"}, {\"start\": 267.32, \"end\": 273.5, \"text\": \"Critics slammed it as racist.\"}, {\"start\": 273.72, \"end\": 284.0, \"text\": \"Chance the Rapper tweeted it was \\\"terribly racist\\\" and others agreed with him.\"}, {\"start\": 284.0, \"end\": 288.72, \"text\": \"Heineken responded by pulling the ad from TV and the internet.\"}, {\"start\": 288.72, \"end\": 297.1, \"text\": \"A spokesman for Heineken said: \\\"While we feel the ad is referencing our Heineken Light beer,\"}, {\"start\": 297.1, \"end\": 304.92, \"text\": \"and that light beer is better than other high-calorie options, we missed the mark.\"}, {\"start\": 304.92, \"end\": 313.6, \"text\": \"We are taking the feedback to heart and will use this to influence future ad campaigns.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 316.2, \"end\": 323.36, \"text\": \"Prom is a tradition no teenager should miss.\"}, {\"start\": 323.44, \"end\": 335.74, \"text\": \"So when Skylar Fontaine of New Orleans learned her Marine boyfriend, Gage, would miss the\"}, {\"start\": 335.74, \"end\": 337.5, \"text\": \"event, she was crushed.\"}, {\"start\": 337.5, \"end\": 350.46, \"text\": \"But thankfully heroes come in all sizes.\"}, {\"start\": 350.46, \"end\": 360.16, \"text\": \"Gage's 2-year-old brother, Clay Jr., stepped up to fill in as Skylar's date.\"}, {\"start\": 360.16, \"end\": 368.42, \"text\": \"Skylar was even able to find a tiny Marine uniform for Clay Jr.\"}, {\"start\": 368.46, \"end\": 379.12, \"text\": \"The paired didn't actually go to the dance but posed for pictures, which have since gone viral.\"}, {\"start\": 379.12, \"end\": 386.04, \"text\": \"Skylar said the adorable gesture made her feel like her boyfriend Gage was home.\"}, {\"start\": 388.58, \"end\": 399.84, \"text\": \"Tax experts say about 80% of people filing taxes will get money back this year.\"}, {\"start\": 399.88, \"end\": 405.3, \"text\": \"And many people already know what they  are going to do with that cash even before it comes.\"}, {\"start\": 405.3, \"end\": 414.84, \"text\": \"According to a SunTrust Bank survey 22% of tax refund money will go towards travel and\"}, {\"start\": 414.86, \"end\": 426.6, \"text\": \"entertainment, 18% towards things like groceries and clothing and 13% on home improvements.\"}, {\"start\": 426.6, \"end\": 433.44, \"text\": \"But the majority of the money, 47%, will go towards savings and paying off debt.\"}, {\"start\": 433.44, \"end\": 439.16, \"text\": \"Money experts say immediately move your refund out of your checking account and into your\"}, {\"start\": 439.18, \"end\": 445.54, \"text\": \"savings so you're not tempted to splurge.\"}, {\"start\": 445.64, \"end\": 449.8, \"text\": \"So... are you getting a tax refund this year?\"}, {\"start\": 449.94, \"end\": 453.64, \"text\": \"If so, how do you plan on spending it?\"}, {\"start\": 453.64, \"end\": 457.12, \"text\": \"Let us know on our Facebook page.\"}, {\"start\": 457.12, \"end\": 461.59, \"text\": \"You can either type in your comment or send us a video.\"}, {\"start\": 461.59, \"end\": 467.8, \"text\": \"We will share some of the responses in our broadcast.\"}, {\"start\": 471.38, \"end\": 473.9, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 473.9, \"end\": 475.6, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 475.6, \"end\": 478.62, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 478.66, \"end\": 485.42, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 485.42, \"end\": 493.58, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "kaRAnvHYY9c": {
    "video_id": "kaRAnvHYY9c",
    "title": "Biden: would \"beat the hell\" out of Trump if in high school  (ASL - 3.22.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180323",
    "duration": 103,
    "view_count": 183,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.9, \"end\": 12.34, \"text\": \"Former Vice President Joe Biden is getting some flak for a speech he made at the University\"}, {\"start\": 12.34, \"end\": 15.6, \"text\": \"of Miami in South Florida on Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 15.6, \"end\": 23.12, \"text\": \"He was talking to the college Democrats about the Access Hollywood video of Trump that surfaced\"}, {\"start\": 23.12, \"end\": 28.58, \"text\": \"in 2016, in which Trump made lewd comments about women.\"}, {\"start\": 28.58, \"end\": 35.76, \"text\": \"Biden said: \\\"A guy who ended up becoming our national leader said I can grab a woman anywhere\"}, {\"start\": 35.76, \"end\": 38.26, \"text\": \"and she likes it.\"}, {\"start\": 38.26, \"end\": 42.5, \"text\": \"And then said, I made a mistake.\"}, {\"start\": 42.5, \"end\": 48.88, \"text\": \"They asked me would I like to debate this gentleman and I said no.\"}, {\"start\": 48.88, \"end\": 59.6, \"text\": \"I said, \\\"If we were in high school I'd take him behind the gym and \\\"beat the hell\\\" out of him.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 59.6, \"end\": 62.64, \"text\": \"I've been in a lot of locker rooms my whole life.\"}, {\"start\": 62.64, \"end\": 64.48, \"text\": \"I'm a pretty damn good athlete.\"}, {\"start\": 64.48, \"end\": 73.4, \"text\": \"Any guy that talked that way was usually the fattest, ugliest SOB in the room.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 73.4, \"end\": 79.28, \"text\": \"President Trump immediately flexed his muscles -- on Twitter, of course-- by tweeting:\"}, {\"start\": 79.28, \"end\": 83.32, \"text\": \"\\\"Crazy Joe Biden is trying to act like a tough guy.\"}, {\"start\": 83.32, \"end\": 88.08, \"text\": \"Actually, he is weak, both mentally and physically, and yet he threatens me, for the second time,\"}, {\"start\": 88.08, \"end\": 90.12, \"text\": \"with physical assault.\"}, {\"start\": 90.12, \"end\": 97.24, \"text\": \"He doesn't know me, but he would go down fast and hard, crying all the way.\"}, {\"start\": 97.4, \"end\": 101.32, \"text\": \"Don't threaten people Joe!\\\"\"}]"
  },
  "UDktJ0JF6Ko": {
    "video_id": "UDktJ0JF6Ko",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.19.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180220",
    "duration": 645,
    "view_count": 2235,
    "description": "2.19.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Nikolas Cruz heavily guarded during court appearance\n-Teens host “lie-in” in front of White House\n-Trump open to improving gun background checks\n-Trump slams Oprah Winfrey’s “60 Minutes” segment\n-Japan’s Olympic star called “Michael Jackson on ice\"\n-Keeping fit without the gym \n-Toy Fair in NYC include poop and zit popping game\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered w",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.08, \"end\": 9.82, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.82, \"end\": 12.42, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 12.42, \"end\": 13.98, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.98, \"end\": 17.44, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.52, \"end\": 29.44, \"text\": \"Florida high school shooter Nikolas Cruz made his second court appearance today in Fort\"}, {\"start\": 29.44, \"end\": 32.98, \"text\": \"Lauderdale.\"}, {\"start\": 32.98, \"end\": 40.28, \"text\": \"As he walked into the courtroom, he was surrounded by several armed deputies.\"}, {\"start\": 40.32, \"end\": 46.58, \"text\": \"From the moment he walked into the courtroom to the moment he left, he never once looked\"}, {\"start\": 46.58, \"end\": 48.54, \"text\": \"up or said anything.\"}, {\"start\": 48.54, \"end\": 53.1, \"text\": \"The hearing lasted about 15 minutes.\"}, {\"start\": 53.1, \"end\": 62.18, \"text\": \"Cruz's attorneys were asking the judge to keep any documents regarding their access\"}, {\"start\": 62.18, \"end\": 64.1, \"text\": \"to Cruz sealed.\"}, {\"start\": 64.1, \"end\": 67.32, \"text\": \"The judge agreed.\"}, {\"start\": 70.32, \"end\": 79.1, \"text\": \"A group of DC teens assembled outside the White House Monday for a three minute lie-in\"}, {\"start\": 79.1, \"end\": 85.08, \"text\": \"for gun reform.\"}, {\"start\": 85.08, \"end\": 94.64, \"text\": \"The lie-in lasted three minutes to represent the length of the shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 94.64, \"end\": 106.92, \"text\": \"The protest represented the 17 victims of the school shooting at Marjory Stoneman Douglas\"}, {\"start\": 106.92, \"end\": 108.06, \"text\": \"high school in Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 108.06, \"end\": 115.24, \"text\": \"The teens hope the demonstration will serve as a visual reminder of the massacre and a\"}, {\"start\": 115.24, \"end\": 118.78, \"text\": \"call to action for gun law reform.\"}, {\"start\": 121.46, \"end\": 134.46, \"text\": \"White House Press Secretary Raj Shah released a statement Monday saying President Trump\"}, {\"start\": 134.46, \"end\": 146.42, \"text\": \"is now in favor of improving the background check system for gun sales and is beginning\"}, {\"start\": 146.42, \"end\": 149.04, \"text\": \"bipartisan talks to change gun sale regulation.\"}, {\"start\": 149.68, \"end\": 154.58, \"text\": \"According to the statement, Trump met with Texas Republican John Cornyn and Connecticut\"}, {\"start\": 154.58, \"end\": 169.7, \"text\": \"Democrat Chris Murphy about a bill to strengthen the way state and federal agencies report offenses.\"}, {\"start\": 169.7, \"end\": 178.8, \"text\": \"These changes could prevent some people from buying guns, especially those with mental illnesses.\"}, {\"start\": 182.52, \"end\": 195.1, \"text\": \"Last fall Oprah Winfrey interviewed 14 Michigan voters, seven of whom voted for Donald Trump\"}, {\"start\": 195.1, \"end\": 198.74, \"text\": \"and seven who did not.\"}, {\"start\": 198.74, \"end\": 210.72, \"text\": \"Last night on \\\"60 Minutes,\\\" she sat down with the voters again to get their thoughts on\"}, {\"start\": 210.72, \"end\": 216.52, \"text\": \"Trump's first year.\"}, {\"start\": 216.52, \"end\": 225.44, \"text\": \"The discussion looked at whether pro-Trump supporters still backed Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 225.44, \"end\": 238.96, \"text\": \"Right after the program aired, Trump tweeted this:\"}, {\"start\": 238.96, \"end\": 251.58, \"text\": \"\\\"Just watched a very insecure Oprah Winfrey, who at one point I knew very well, interview\"}, {\"start\": 251.58, \"end\": 253.959, \"text\": \"a panel of people on \\\"60 Minutes.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 253.959, \"end\": 261.1, \"text\": \"Questions were biased and slanted, the facts incorrect.\"}, {\"start\": 261.1, \"end\": 268.68, \"text\": \"Hope Oprah runs [for president] so she can be exposed and defeated just like all of the\"}, {\"start\": 268.68, \"end\": 271.5, \"text\": \"others!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 276.22, \"end\": 289.22, \"text\": \"Last night 23-year-old Japanese figure skater Yuzuru Hanyu won his second Olympic gold in\"}, {\"start\": 289.22, \"end\": 292.16, \"text\": \"the winter Olympics.\"}, {\"start\": 292.16, \"end\": 300.6, \"text\": \"He is the first male figure skater since 1952 to win back-to-back gold medals and now his\"}, {\"start\": 300.6, \"end\": 305.68, \"text\": \"popularity has shot through the roof.\"}, {\"start\": 305.68, \"end\": 317.02, \"text\": \"His performances are the perfect combination of grace and fury.\"}, {\"start\": 317.02, \"end\": 327.16, \"text\": \"Because of his jaw-dropping athleticism combined with enchanting artistry and a commanding\"}, {\"start\": 327.16, \"end\": 334.88, \"text\": \"presence, some say he's like watching Michael Jackson on ice.\"}, {\"start\": 334.88, \"end\": 340.12, \"text\": \"Fans both young and old are mesmerized by his skating.\"}, {\"start\": 340.12, \"end\": 344.259, \"text\": \"Some fans prayed before he hit the ice.\"}, {\"start\": 344.26, \"end\": 350.32, \"text\": \"Others were moved to tears.\"}, {\"start\": 350.32, \"end\": 359.02, \"text\": \"After his historic win last night, many fans celebrated by throwing stuffed Winnie the\"}, {\"start\": 359.02, \"end\": 361.46, \"text\": \"Pooh bears on the ice.\"}, {\"start\": 361.56, \"end\": 371.52, \"text\": \"The good luck charm has been Yuzuru's favorite since he was a kid.\"}, {\"start\": 371.52, \"end\": 378.5, \"text\": \"Some are calling the 23-year-old the greatest figure skater of all time.\"}, {\"start\": 381.34, \"end\": 388.26, \"text\": \"Everyone knows exercise leads to a healthier life.\"}, {\"start\": 388.26, \"end\": 393.52, \"text\": \"But what if you hate the gym?\"}, {\"start\": 393.52, \"end\": 405.54, \"text\": \"If that describes you, there is still plenty of ways to stay fit.\"}, {\"start\": 405.54, \"end\": 415.4, \"text\": \"Here are some tips from the US Department of Agriculture.\"}, {\"start\": 415.52, \"end\": 416.319, \"text\": \"Get social.\"}, {\"start\": 416.32, \"end\": 423.34, \"text\": \"Instead of going out to eat with friends, pick a group activity instead.\"}, {\"start\": 423.34, \"end\": 434.56, \"text\": \"Go for a hike, take a walk or play an exercise-based video game.\"}, {\"start\": 434.56, \"end\": 443.44, \"text\": \"Find ways to move at work.\"}, {\"start\": 443.44, \"end\": 457.28, \"text\": \"If you can use a standing desk, you can stand during phone calls\"}, {\"start\": 457.28, \"end\": 465.38, \"text\": \"or choose a printer further away from your desk.\"}, {\"start\": 465.38, \"end\": 470.94, \"text\": \"Do something new.\"}, {\"start\": 470.94, \"end\": 480.16, \"text\": \"A new skill or unusual activity can kickstart your motivation.\"}, {\"start\": 480.16, \"end\": 485.8, \"text\": \"Try dance class or sign up for a sports league.\"}, {\"start\": 485.8, \"end\": 487.54, \"text\": \"Dive in!\"}, {\"start\": 487.54, \"end\": 493.68, \"text\": \"If you don't like to sweat in the heat, head for the water.\"}, {\"start\": 493.68, \"end\": 499.979, \"text\": \"Take a swim at a community pool or sign up for a water aerobics class.\"}, {\"start\": 499.979, \"end\": 501.77, \"text\": \"Stay on track.\"}, {\"start\": 501.77, \"end\": 509.68, \"text\": \"Keep track of your activity and the food you eat with wearable technology or take advantage\"}, {\"start\": 509.68, \"end\": 513.02, \"text\": \"of tracking sites online.\"}, {\"start\": 516.5, \"end\": 531.84, \"text\": \"New York is hosting \\\"Toy Fair 2018\\\" and gross toys are in this year!\"}, {\"start\": 531.84, \"end\": 541.46, \"text\": \"\\\"Poo Dough\\\" looks like the real thing, but without the smell.\"}, {\"start\": 541.46, \"end\": 553.46, \"text\": \"You can shape the perfect poop with two different shades of brown dough.\"}, {\"start\": 553.46, \"end\": 570.1, \"text\": \"\\\"Pop-A-Zit\\\" requires players to roll the dice and squeeze a bright red button on the forehead\"}, {\"start\": 570.14, \"end\": 572.4, \"text\": \"of the face-shape board.\"}, {\"start\": 572.4, \"end\": 578.58, \"text\": \"You never know when the zit will pop.\"}, {\"start\": 578.58, \"end\": 588.4, \"text\": \"There is the \\\"Toilet Paper Blaster\\\" which is like a Super Soaker, only this one fires\"}, {\"start\": 588.4, \"end\": 591.88, \"text\": \"fresh toilet paper spit wads.\"}, {\"start\": 591.88, \"end\": 606.24, \"text\": \"And finally there is \\\"Snot It\\\" where you use nose glasses to pick up as many snot pieces\"}, {\"start\": 606.24, \"end\": 607.72, \"text\": \"as you can.\"}, {\"start\": 607.72, \"end\": 615.54, \"text\": \"The new toys are scheduled to hit the shelves in the fall.\"}, {\"start\": 618.78, \"end\": 621.84, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 621.84, \"end\": 623.58, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 623.58, \"end\": 626.24, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 626.24, \"end\": 631.94, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 631.94, \"end\": 637.38, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "55KLzfK4fqg": {
    "video_id": "55KLzfK4fqg",
    "title": "Supreme court declines request to take DACA case (ASL - 2.26.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180227",
    "duration": 54,
    "view_count": 168,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.9, \"end\": 12.76, \"text\": \"On Monday the Supreme Court said it will stay out of the dispute over the Deferred Action\"}, {\"start\": 12.76, \"end\": 14.7, \"text\": \"for Childhood Arrivals (DACA) program -- for now.\"}, {\"start\": 14.7, \"end\": 28.4, \"text\": \"The justices declined a request from the Trump administration to review a lower court decision\"}, {\"start\": 28.4, \"end\": 34.76, \"text\": \"that temporarily blocked the government's efforts to end the program.\"}, {\"start\": 34.76, \"end\": 40.14, \"text\": \"That means the case will continue in the lower courts.\"}, {\"start\": 40.14, \"end\": 45.98, \"text\": \"And for now, renewals can continue.\"}, {\"start\": 45.98, \"end\": 52.2, \"text\": \"The Trump administration had planned to end the program March 5th.\"}]"
  },
  "_RlJLypK6ok": {
    "video_id": "_RlJLypK6ok",
    "title": "Sign1News 8.10.20",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20200810",
    "duration": 770,
    "view_count": 1375,
    "description": "Sign1News, a leading deaf news source, uses American Sign Language to cover the top news stories of the week about children testing positive for COVID-19, looting in Chicago, and Trump's latest executive action.\n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES: \n\n- Nearly 100,000 children test positive in two weeks\n- Violence, looting erupts in Chicago\n- Trump's executive actions spark confusion\n- Celebrity chef's home breaks out in fire\n- 103-year-old woman gets tattoo",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 10.26, \"end\": 12.54, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 12.54, \"end\": 16.86, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 16.86, \"end\": 18.72, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 18.72, \"end\": 22.28, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 29.16, \"end\": 36.8, \"text\": \"Early Sunday the US reached another grim milestone.\"}, {\"start\": 36.8, \"end\": 45.46, \"text\": \"The country topped five million cases of coronavirus.\"}, {\"start\": 45.46, \"end\": 54.2, \"text\": \"That's the official count from Johns Hopkins University.\"}, {\"start\": 54.2, \"end\": 64.74, \"text\": \"However experts believe the true number of infections is likely much higher.\"}, {\"start\": 64.74, \"end\": 76.14, \"text\": \"The US now holds about a quarter of the total cases reported globally and also tops the\"}, {\"start\": 76.14, \"end\": 79.58, \"text\": \"list with the most reported deaths in the world, desk in the world,\"}, {\"start\": 79.58, \"end\": 84.92, \"text\": \"more than 162-thousand fatalities.\"}, {\"start\": 84.92, \"end\": 87.84, \"text\": \"And that's not the only dire statistic.\"}, {\"start\": 87.84, \"end\": 97.92, \"text\": \"More than 97-thousand children tested positive for coronavirus in the last two weeks of July.\"}, {\"start\": 97.92, \"end\": 104.54, \"text\": \"That's according to a medical report published by the American Academy of Pediatrics and\"}, {\"start\": 104.54, \"end\": 111.14, \"text\": \"the Children's Hospital Association.\"}, {\"start\": 111.14, \"end\": 116.48, \"text\": \"The report say in those two weeks there was a 40-percent increase in child cases across\"}, {\"start\": 116.48, \"end\": 124.64, \"text\": \"states and cities that were studied.\"}, {\"start\": 124.64, \"end\": 130.18, \"text\": \"The age range for children differed by state, with some defining children as only those\"}, {\"start\": 130.18, \"end\": 138.34, \"text\": \"up to age 14 and Alabama pushing the limit to 24.\"}, {\"start\": 138.34, \"end\": 142.6, \"text\": \"The compiled data comes during back-to-school season as health officials are trying to understand\"}, {\"start\": 142.6, \"end\": 152.5, \"text\": \"the effects of the virus on children and the role young play in its spread.\"}, {\"start\": 155.64, \"end\": 167.5, \"text\": \"Police clashed with crowds overnight in downtown Chicago as looting and vandalism erupted in\"}, {\"start\": 167.5, \"end\": 169.68, \"text\": \"the retail district.\"}, {\"start\": 169.68, \"end\": 175.46, \"text\": \"Chicago police say crowds began to gather around midnight.\"}, {\"start\": 175.46, \"end\": 187.68, \"text\": \"Windows were broken at multiple stores including Saks Fifth Avenue and the Coach Store.\"}, {\"start\": 187.68, \"end\": 199.18, \"text\": \"According to police superintendent David Brown Monday more than 100 people were arrested.\"}, {\"start\": 199.18, \"end\": 201.88, \"text\": \"Thirteen officers were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 201.88, \"end\": 209.7, \"text\": \"It wasn't immediately clear what started the unrest but the Chicago Tribune Reports that\"}, {\"start\": 209.7, \"end\": 215.86, \"text\": \"anti-police graffiti was seen.\"}, {\"start\": 215.86, \"end\": 225.12, \"text\": \"Brown believes the unrest was related to an officer-involved shooting that happened earlier Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 225.12, \"end\": 233.56, \"text\": \"Police say there was a great deal of misinformation regarding the incident.\"}, {\"start\": 233.56, \"end\": 245.12, \"text\": \"Crowds had faced off with police after officers shot and wounded a suspect on Chicago's South Side.\"}, {\"start\": 245.12, \"end\": 252.66, \"text\": \"Police said in a statement they had received a call that a person had a gun.\"}, {\"start\": 252.66, \"end\": 256.54, \"text\": \"When they arrived the man ran away and began firing at officers.\"}, {\"start\": 256.54, \"end\": 259.24, \"text\": \"The statement said police returned fire.\"}, {\"start\": 259.24, \"end\": 269.66, \"text\": \"The suspect was hospitalized but information on his condition is unknown.\"}, {\"start\": 269.66, \"end\": 275.92, \"text\": \"According to Chicago police, shortly after the shooting crowds gathered with \\\"emotions\"}, {\"start\": 275.92, \"end\": 278.76, \"text\": \"running high\\\" and clashed with police.\"}, {\"start\": 278.76, \"end\": 289.24, \"text\": \"According to police, one officer suffered a hurt shoulder and one was sprayed with mace.\"}, {\"start\": 289.24, \"end\": 297.34, \"text\": \"Brown says police will maintain a heavy presence downtown until further notice.\"}, {\"start\": 300.36, \"end\": 309.4, \"text\": \"As the pandemic continues many families are finding themselves struggling to make ends meet.\"}, {\"start\": 311.16, \"end\": 319.6, \"text\": \"In an effort to ease their burden, Saturday, President Trump signed four new executive actions.\"}, {\"start\": 319.6, \"end\": 336.04, \"text\": \"The four-part executive actions includes 400-dollars in unemployment benefits, a payroll tax holiday\"}, {\"start\": 336.04, \"end\": 345.98, \"text\": \"for Americans earning less than 100-thousand a year, an executive order on eviction and\"}, {\"start\": 345.98, \"end\": 351.42, \"text\": \"deferment of student loans.\"}, {\"start\": 351.42, \"end\": 361.68, \"text\": \"But some lawmakers say Trump's move does not provide a clear path to help millions of Americans\"}, {\"start\": 361.68, \"end\": 364.12, \"text\": \"out of work.\"}, {\"start\": 364.12, \"end\": 370.12, \"text\": \"So what do the actions really mean for the average American?\"}, {\"start\": 370.12, \"end\": 372.6, \"text\": \"Let's break these down.\"}, {\"start\": 372.6, \"end\": 376.84, \"text\": \"First up: an additional 400 dollars in unemployment benefits.\"}, {\"start\": 376.84, \"end\": 381.32, \"text\": \"At first Trump said states would have to chip in for the aid by paying the first 100.\"}, {\"start\": 381.32, \"end\": 386.16, \"text\": \"Then the federal government would add 300.\"}, {\"start\": 386.16, \"end\": 393.72, \"text\": \"But now he says some states may not be required to pay part of the benefits, if governors\"}, {\"start\": 393.72, \"end\": 397.12, \"text\": \"request federal help.\"}, {\"start\": 397.12, \"end\": 401.86, \"text\": \"Some lawmakers are concerned if states have the money.\"}, {\"start\": 401.86, \"end\": 409.74, \"text\": \"A White House economic advisor says states have not spent all the money that was allocated\"}, {\"start\": 409.74, \"end\": 413.2, \"text\": \"to them.\"}, {\"start\": 413.2, \"end\": 423.12, \"text\": \"But House Speaker Nancy Pelosi says states don't have the money because they have expenses\"}, {\"start\": 423.12, \"end\": 432.06, \"text\": \"from the coronavirus and have lost revenue.\"}, {\"start\": 432.06, \"end\": 440.02, \"text\": \"Up next: an executive order on eviction.\"}, {\"start\": 440.02, \"end\": 449.76, \"text\": \"In reality Trump's executive action does not explicitly provide funds to help homeowners and renters.\"}, {\"start\": 449.76, \"end\": 460.72, \"text\": \"The action calls for the Housing and Urban Development and Treasury secretaries to identify\"}, {\"start\": 460.72, \"end\": 465.28, \"text\": \"\\\"all federal funds to provide temporary financial assistance\\\" to those who are struggling to\"}, {\"start\": 465.28, \"end\": 472.4, \"text\": \"pay their rents and mortgages because of the coronavirus.\"}, {\"start\": 472.4, \"end\": 481.36, \"text\": \"Experts told CNN it was unclear based on the process laid out for government agencies how\"}, {\"start\": 481.36, \"end\": 487.8, \"text\": \"long it would take anyone to see funding for this.\"}, {\"start\": 487.8, \"end\": 495.48, \"text\": \"Trump also promised to suspend payroll taxes, that's the money paid into Social Security\"}, {\"start\": 495.48, \"end\": 499.06, \"text\": \"and Medicare.\"}, {\"start\": 499.06, \"end\": 510.36, \"text\": \"But Trump's plan is actually a deferral and only Congress has the power to change tax law.\"}, {\"start\": 510.36, \"end\": 525.1, \"text\": \"Sunday Pelosi called the executive actions \\\"unconstitutional\\\" and questioned their effectiveness.\"}, {\"start\": 525.1, \"end\": 533.24, \"text\": \"However other lawmakers are thanking Trump for attempting to do something about the stimulus\"}, {\"start\": 533.24, \"end\": 536.2, \"text\": \"package deal that still hasn't been reached.\"}, {\"start\": 540.52, \"end\": 551.46, \"text\": \"Sunday a fire broke at celebrity chef Rachael Ray's home in New York.\"}, {\"start\": 551.46, \"end\": 559.44, \"text\": \"According to People Magazine, Ray, her husband and their dog are all safe.\"}, {\"start\": 559.44, \"end\": 569.12, \"text\": \"A representative for Ray says the house suffered damage, although no word yet on the extent.\"}, {\"start\": 569.12, \"end\": 576.76, \"text\": \"Hours prior to the fire, Ray shared pictures of the meal she and her friends were having\"}, {\"start\": 576.76, \"end\": 580.44, \"text\": \"during a golf outing.\"}, {\"start\": 580.44, \"end\": 589.74, \"text\": \"Ray has been making meals in her home since the Covid-19 pandemic broke out.\"}, {\"start\": 592.9, \"end\": 598.44, \"text\": \"Call her biker granny.\"}, {\"start\": 598.44, \"end\": 606.12, \"text\": \"Michigan woman Dorothy Pollack got her first tattoo to mark her 103rd birthday!\"}, {\"start\": 606.12, \"end\": 611.68, \"text\": \"She decided to check off some bucket list items after spending months in isolation during\"}, {\"start\": 611.68, \"end\": 624.74, \"text\": \"a coronavirus lockdown at a nursing home.\"}, {\"start\": 624.74, \"end\": 632.38, \"text\": \"She says weeks after being discharged, out of nowhere she decided she wanted a tattoo.\"}, {\"start\": 632.38, \"end\": 641.8, \"text\": \"The grandmother got a tattoo of a frog, the one thing she loves more than beer and burgers.\"}, {\"start\": 641.8, \"end\": 652.28, \"text\": \"The tattoo artist says she took the needle like a champ and he didn't even flinch once.\"}, {\"start\": 652.28, \"end\": 656.86, \"text\": \"She says she absolutely loves her new ink.\"}, {\"start\": 656.86, \"end\": 664.02, \"text\": \"After the tattoo Pollack also crossed riding on a motorcycle off her list.\"}, {\"start\": 668.78, \"end\": 670.38, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 670.38, \"end\": 671.66, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 671.66, \"end\": 673.68, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News live.\"}, {\"start\": 673.68, \"end\": 681.5, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our\"}, {\"start\": 681.5, \"end\": 683.02, \"text\": \"app too.\"}, {\"start\": 683.02, \"end\": 687.54, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "7ztoTdD13xM": {
    "video_id": "7ztoTdD13xM",
    "title": "Nature lovers watch eaglets being hatched (ASL 12.28.17)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171229",
    "duration": 60,
    "view_count": 58,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.6, \"end\": 8.72, \"text\": \"A female bald eagle named \\\"Harriett\\\" has been nesting in North Fort Myers since 2006.\"}, {\"start\": 8.72, \"end\": 15.0, \"text\": \"Finally, the eaglets hatched from the two eggs she laid in November.\"}, {\"start\": 15.0, \"end\": 26.94, \"text\": \"Thousands of nature lovers watched via WebCam as the baby eagles hatched.\"}, {\"start\": 26.94, \"end\": 34.56, \"text\": \"\\\"E-10\\\" came into the world on Tuesday at about 8:45 PM.\"}, {\"start\": 34.56, \"end\": 42.22, \"text\": \"\\\"E-11\\\" came into the world just before 4:30 PM Wednesday afternoon.\"}, {\"start\": 42.22, \"end\": 52.26, \"text\": \"Harriett's original mate, Ozzie, died in 2015.\"}, {\"start\": 52.26, \"end\": 58.92, \"text\": \"She is now in her second meeting season with her new mate, known as M-15.\"}]"
  },
  "lcv4YNHjvsc": {
    "video_id": "lcv4YNHjvsc",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.10.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180210",
    "duration": 626,
    "view_count": 1857,
    "description": "2.10.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-White House denies release of Democrats' response memo\n-Police look for woman who left newborn at airport\n-Dad who lunged at Nassar donates fundraiser money\n-CDC releases grim flu report\n-\"House of Cards\" actor Reg Cathey dies at 59\n-What happened to the Tesla shot into space?\n-Facebook testing a \"downvote\" button\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.8, \"end\": 7.8, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.8, \"end\": 9.8, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.8, \"end\": 11.4, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.4, \"end\": 14.32, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.48, \"end\": 25.76, \"text\": \"Last week President Trump allowed the release of a controversial Republican memo that claims\"}, {\"start\": 25.76, \"end\": 36.36, \"text\": \"the FBI abused its surveillance privileges during the 2016 presidential election.\"}, {\"start\": 36.36, \"end\": 46.64, \"text\": \"Trump said the memo cleared his name of any suspicion in the Russia investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 46.64, \"end\": 52.14, \"text\": \"But on Friday Trump blocked the release of the Democratic memo regarding the FBI and\"}, {\"start\": 52.14, \"end\": 57.46, \"text\": \"the 2016 election.\"}, {\"start\": 57.46, \"end\": 65.26, \"text\": \"The White House says Trump wants to release the Democrats' memo, but cannot, because it\"}, {\"start\": 65.26, \"end\": 71.28, \"text\": \"contains \\\"classified and especially sensitive passages.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 71.28, \"end\": 79.6, \"text\": \"The White House went on to encourage the House Intelligence Committee to revise the memo\"}, {\"start\": 79.6, \"end\": 81.62, \"text\": \"with the assistance of the Justice Department.\"}, {\"start\": 81.62, \"end\": 90.76, \"text\": \"Democrats in Washington are criticizing the president's decision saying it is hypocrisy,\"}, {\"start\": 90.76, \"end\": 98.14, \"text\": \"obstruction of justice and a blatant political move.\"}, {\"start\": 101.4, \"end\": 107.54, \"text\": \"Authorities in Tucson, Arizona are looking for this woman.\"}, {\"start\": 107.54, \"end\": 111.62, \"text\": \"Take a good look.\"}, {\"start\": 111.62, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"On Thursday police say they received a 911 call about an abandoned newborn baby.\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 128.22, \"text\": \"The caller said someone left the child with a note in a bathroom and he was wrapped in\"}, {\"start\": 128.22, \"end\": 130.46, \"text\": \"a blanket.\"}, {\"start\": 130.56, \"end\": 138.0, \"text\": \"Airport security immediately started searching the airport surveillance video.\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 146.54, \"text\": \"Authorities believe the woman gave birth inside the airport, carried the baby to a family\"}, {\"start\": 146.54, \"end\": 154.66, \"text\": \"changing room in the baggage claim area and abandoned the infant on a changing table with\"}, {\"start\": 154.66, \"end\": 159.92, \"text\": \"a note.\"}, {\"start\": 159.96, \"end\": 166.08, \"text\": \"The first part of the note appears to be written from the newborn's perspective.\"}, {\"start\": 166.08, \"end\": 167.56, \"text\": \"It said: \\\"Please help me.\"}, {\"start\": 167.56, \"end\": 170.7, \"text\": \"My mom had no idea she was pregnant.\"}, {\"start\": 170.78, \"end\": 173.58, \"text\": \"She is unable and unfit to take care of me.\"}, {\"start\": 173.58, \"end\": 179.88, \"text\": \"Please get me to the authorities so they can find me a good home.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 179.88, \"end\": 184.4, \"text\": \"The second half of the note appears to be the mother's plea, saying: \\\"I just want who\"}, {\"start\": 184.4, \"end\": 189.56, \"text\": \"is best for him and it is not me.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 189.56, \"end\": 198.08, \"text\": \"The woman remains unidentified and criminal charges have yet to be determined.\"}, {\"start\": 198.08, \"end\": 204.3, \"text\": \"The baby is under the custody of the State Department of Child Safety.\"}, {\"start\": 207.94, \"end\": 228.2, \"text\": \"Last week Randall Margraves made national headlines as the father that launched at convicted\"}, {\"start\": 228.2, \"end\": 230.04, \"text\": \"sexual predator Larry Nassar.\"}, {\"start\": 230.04, \"end\": 240.02, \"text\": \"Nassar molested his three daughters.\"}, {\"start\": 240.02, \"end\": 249.68, \"text\": \"Right after that incident an online fundraiser popped up to help Margraves with any possible\"}, {\"start\": 249.68, \"end\": 252.52, \"text\": \"legal expenses.\"}, {\"start\": 252.52, \"end\": 257.72, \"text\": \"Thirty-one thousand dollars was raised in six days.\"}, {\"start\": 257.72, \"end\": 263.0, \"text\": \"But Margraves released a statement that said he did not need the money and will instead\"}, {\"start\": 263.0, \"end\": 272.18, \"text\": \"donate the funds to local charities that assist survivors of sexual assault.\"}, {\"start\": 272.3, \"end\": 278.32, \"text\": \"Margraves has not been charged with any crime over his court outburst.\"}, {\"start\": 278.42, \"end\": 285.42, \"text\": \"His attorney said he's working to ensure that no charges arise from Margraves' actions.\"}, {\"start\": 289.34, \"end\": 292.4, \"text\": \"The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention released new numbers this week on flu activity\"}, {\"start\": 292.4, \"end\": 295.2, \"text\": \"across the country and the report is grim.\"}, {\"start\": 295.2, \"end\": 302.24, \"text\": \"Officials say the flu has hit just about every state in the country, as well as Puerto Rico.\"}, {\"start\": 302.32, \"end\": 305.32, \"text\": \"And the death toll is rising.\"}, {\"start\": 305.32, \"end\": 310.34, \"text\": \"This week 10 more children died, bringing the total number of children killed by the\"}, {\"start\": 310.38, \"end\": 313.68, \"text\": \"flu to 63.\"}, {\"start\": 313.68, \"end\": 320.9, \"text\": \"The CDC reports hospitalizations have also been increasing over the past five weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 320.9, \"end\": 327.62, \"text\": \"To make matters worse, the CDC says this flu season has not yet reached its peak.\"}, {\"start\": 327.62, \"end\": 334.94, \"text\": \"Experts say to watch for some critical symptoms that could indicate a severe infection including\"}, {\"start\": 334.94, \"end\": 346.4, \"text\": \"a persistent high fever, difficulty breathing or shortness of breath, rapid heartbeat and\"}, {\"start\": 346.5, \"end\": 349.98, \"text\": \"extreme tiredness.\"}, {\"start\": 350.1, \"end\": 358.66, \"text\": \"The CDC recommends beginning antivirals as soon as symptoms appear and take necessary\"}, {\"start\": 358.66, \"end\": 365.54, \"text\": \"steps to prevent spreading the illness like getting the flu shot, washing your hands and\"}, {\"start\": 365.54, \"end\": 370.94, \"text\": \"most important, if you're ill, stay home!\"}, {\"start\": 370.94, \"end\": 375.94, \"text\": \"Don't spread your virus around by going to work or school.\"}, {\"start\": 375.94, \"end\": 386.84, \"text\": \"The CDC says it is important to note that what may be mild symptoms to you could be\"}, {\"start\": 386.84, \"end\": 391.18, \"text\": \"deadly for someone else.\"}, {\"start\": 393.96, \"end\": 410.64, \"text\": \"Reg E. Cathey, who won an Emmy for the role of \\\"Freddy\\\" in the Netflix series \\\"House of\"}, {\"start\": 410.64, \"end\": 414.08, \"text\": \"Cards,\\\" has died at age 59.\"}, {\"start\": 414.08, \"end\": 424.26, \"text\": \"TMZ reports he had been battling lung cancer and died at his New York home surrounded by\"}, {\"start\": 424.26, \"end\": 428.0, \"text\": \"family and friends.\"}, {\"start\": 428.0, \"end\": 436.72, \"text\": \"He's also known for his roles on \\\"The Wire\\\" and \\\"Oz.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 436.72, \"end\": 448.66, \"text\": \"The creator of \\\"The Wire,\\\" David Simon, first reported Cathey's death on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 451.24, \"end\": 469.34, \"text\": \"On Tuesday Space-X launched a red sports car into orbit with a mannequin named \\\"Starman\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 469.42, \"end\": 472.46, \"text\": \"behind the wheel.\"}, {\"start\": 472.46, \"end\": 480.2, \"text\": \"But where exactly is the car going?\"}, {\"start\": 480.2, \"end\": 495.62, \"text\": \"NASA's jet propulsion laboratory expects \\\"Starman\\\" to take this path as he orbits the sun.\"}, {\"start\": 495.62, \"end\": 503.84, \"text\": \"The farthest he'll get is about 155 million miles from the sun.\"}, {\"start\": 503.84, \"end\": 510.2, \"text\": \"That's about the same distance as Mars gets from the sun.\"}, {\"start\": 510.2, \"end\": 520.06, \"text\": \"Experts say the current projections could change, as forces such as radiation could\"}, {\"start\": 520.06, \"end\": 524.96, \"text\": \"slowly steer the roadster onto a different course.\"}, {\"start\": 528.86, \"end\": 538.1, \"text\": \"Facebook users have been clamoring for a \\\"dislike\\\" button for years.\"}, {\"start\": 538.1, \"end\": 549.04, \"text\": \"According to multiple news reports, Facebook is testing a \\\"down vote\\\" button instead.\"}, {\"start\": 549.04, \"end\": 557.36, \"text\": \"Users can signal to Facebook a comment that they believe is offensive, misleading or off-topic\"}, {\"start\": 557.44, \"end\": 560.58, \"text\": \"by using the \\\"down vote\\\" button.\"}, {\"start\": 560.58, \"end\": 575.4, \"text\": \"The button will be tested on 5 percent of Android users in the United States whose language\"}, {\"start\": 575.42, \"end\": 577.02, \"text\": \"is set to English.\"}, {\"start\": 577.02, \"end\": 582.52, \"text\": \"Down voting was made popular by Reddit.\"}, {\"start\": 582.52, \"end\": 592.7, \"text\": \"Reddit founder and CEO Alexis Ohanian tweeted: \\\"Sincerest form of flattery!\"}, {\"start\": 592.7, \"end\": 598.5, \"text\": \"Wish I trademarked it when I came up with it.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 601.78, \"end\": 604.34, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 604.34, \"end\": 605.78, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 605.78, \"end\": 607.94, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 607.94, \"end\": 612.46, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 612.46, \"end\": 618.7, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "ETFBaCv19IQ": {
    "video_id": "ETFBaCv19IQ",
    "title": "Third Nor'easter this month hits New England (ASL - 3.13.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180314",
    "duration": 59,
    "view_count": 72,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.64, \"end\": 10.08, \"text\": \"We're one week away from the first day of spring and the northeast just can't\"}, {\"start\": 10.08, \"end\": 11.76, \"text\": \"catch a break.\"}, {\"start\": 11.76, \"end\": 23.16, \"text\": \"A third coastal storm in less than two weeks will bring more snow, more flooding and howling\"}, {\"start\": 23.16, \"end\": 27.24, \"text\": \"winds to New England, impacting millions.\"}, {\"start\": 27.4, \"end\": 31.52, \"text\": \"Officials are warning people, again, about dangerous driving conditions.\"}, {\"start\": 31.52, \"end\": 39.28, \"text\": \"State governent offices are closed and businesses are being asked to allow their employees to\"}, {\"start\": 39.28, \"end\": 41.6, \"text\": \"stay home.\"}, {\"start\": 41.6, \"end\": 50.88, \"text\": \"Massachusetts' governor is telling non-emergency state employees not to report to work.\"}, {\"start\": 51.28, \"end\": 59.12, \"text\": \"The storm has canceled hundreds of flights and knocked out power for thousands.\"}]"
  },
  "gD1qIg05Rgs": {
    "video_id": "gD1qIg05Rgs",
    "title": "Topless woman protests Italian elections (ASL - 3.4.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180305",
    "duration": 82,
    "view_count": 505,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.86, \"end\": 8.58, \"text\": \"Voting is underway in Italy's unpredictable national election.\"}, {\"start\": 8.58, \"end\": 16.4, \"text\": \"The campaign has been divisive with the issue of immigration front and center.\"}, {\"start\": 16.4, \"end\": 23.76, \"text\": \"Traditional parties on the right and the left are losing ground.\"}, {\"start\": 23.76, \"end\": 37.26, \"text\": \"The Populist Five Star Movement is likely to emerge as the single largest party.\"}, {\"start\": 37.26, \"end\": 47.16, \"text\": \"But no party or group is expected to win the majority needed to form a government.\"}, {\"start\": 47.16, \"end\": 53.86, \"text\": \"There have been protests but none stranger than the one today.\"}, {\"start\": 53.86, \"end\": 64.26, \"text\": \"As former prime minister Silvio Berlusconi was casting his vote for the center-right\"}, {\"start\": 64.26, \"end\": 69.84, \"text\": \"party, a woman popped up from a group of photographers and took off her shirt to reveal\"}, {\"start\": 69.84, \"end\": 78.02, \"text\": \"her bare chest with the words \\\"Berlusconi you are finished!\\\" written on her skin in Italian.\"}, {\"start\": 78.02, \"end\": 81.2, \"text\": \"Berlusconi did not acknowledge the woman's protest and instead walked out of the precinct.\"}]"
  },
  "VYLUoMLnlSs": {
    "video_id": "VYLUoMLnlSs",
    "title": "How does the government shutdown affect you? (ASL - 1.20.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180120",
    "duration": 115,
    "view_count": 295,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 2.54, \"end\": 6.28, \"text\": \"The US government is officially shut down.\"}, {\"start\": 6.28, \"end\": 12.42, \"text\": \"And it falls on the one-year anniversary of Trump's inauguration.\"}, {\"start\": 12.42, \"end\": 17.52, \"text\": \"If you're wondering how the shutdown affects you, here's a breakdown:\"}, {\"start\": 17.52, \"end\": 21.44, \"text\": \"Federal workers will be affected right away.\"}, {\"start\": 21.44, \"end\": 25.4, \"text\": \"During the shutdown, most federal agencies close.\"}, {\"start\": 25.4, \"end\": 30.4, \"text\": \"Hundreds of thousands of workers will be furloughed or take a leave without pay.\"}, {\"start\": 30.4, \"end\": 33.82, \"text\": \"But not all federal workers.\"}, {\"start\": 33.82, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"Those deemed essential will still work: air-traffic controllers, law enforcement, national security\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 43.2, \"text\": \"and federal court staff.\"}, {\"start\": 43.2, \"end\": 48.1, \"text\": \"But they won't be paid until after the shutdown ends.\"}, {\"start\": 48.1, \"end\": 49.96, \"text\": \"And what about the US military?\"}, {\"start\": 49.96, \"end\": 54.84, \"text\": \"The good news is the troops have already been paid for January.\"}, {\"start\": 54.84, \"end\": 58.68, \"text\": \"But a prolonged shutdown would hurt them.\"}, {\"start\": 58.68, \"end\": 61.9, \"text\": \"You will still get your Social Security check.\"}, {\"start\": 61.9, \"end\": 65.1, \"text\": \"That program is mandatory.\"}, {\"start\": 65.1, \"end\": 69.18, \"text\": \"The post office will keep running so your mail will be delivered on time.\"}, {\"start\": 69.18, \"end\": 73.62, \"text\": \"You can also get a new passport, but move quickly.\"}, {\"start\": 73.62, \"end\": 79.42, \"text\": \"Funding will run out if the shutdown drags on.\"}, {\"start\": 79.42, \"end\": 88.92, \"text\": \"You're out of luck if you planned to vacation to a national park, a museum or a monument.\"}, {\"start\": 88.96, \"end\": 95.18, \"text\": \"Taxpayer-funded sites will be closed, but the Trump administration is looking for ways\"}, {\"start\": 95.18, \"end\": 98.6, \"text\": \"to keep limited access where possible.\"}, {\"start\": 98.6, \"end\": 102.98, \"text\": \"So who does get paid during the shutdown?\"}, {\"start\": 102.98, \"end\": 109.9, \"text\": \"Those who have \\\"constitutional duties\\\" like the president, Supreme Court and members of\"}, {\"start\": 109.9, \"end\": 112.92, \"text\": \"Congress.\"}]"
  },
  "yyXX3naOlks": {
    "video_id": "yyXX3naOlks",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.2.17- News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171103",
    "duration": 496,
    "view_count": 85,
    "description": "November 2, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-NYC TERROR ATTACK SUSPECT IN COURT\n-GOP LEADERS UNVEIL TAX REFORM PLAN\n-MANAFORT’S ATTORNEY ARGUES AGAINST HOUSE ARREST\n-WOMAN KIDNAPPED, ESCAPES FROM CAR TRUNK\n-ASTROS FANS CELEBRATE WORLD SERIES WIN\n-HERSHEY’S FIRST NEW CANDY BAR IN 20 YEARS\n-NEW MARVEL COMICS MOVIE\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrou",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 13.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 13.0, \"end\": 15.0, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.0, \"end\": 21.0, \"text\": \"The suspect in the New York City terror\"}, {\"start\": 21.1, \"end\": 27.1, \"text\": \"attacks Sayfullo Saipov\"}, {\"start\": 28.0, \"end\": 34.0, \"text\": \"appeared in federal court this morning.\"}, {\"start\": 34.0, \"end\": 39.0, \"text\": \"He is charged with providing\"}, {\"start\": 39.0, \"end\": 43.0, \"text\": \"material support to ISIS and destruction of\"}, {\"start\": 43.0, \"end\": 48.0, \"text\": \"motor vehicles. Court papers say he intended to use\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"a truck to inflict maximum damage against civilians and\"}, {\"start\": 53.0, \"end\": 58.0, \"text\": \"chose to strike on Halloween because he believed there\"}, {\"start\": 58.0, \"end\": 62.0, \"text\": \"would be more civilians on the street. During the hearing\"}, {\"start\": 63.0, \"end\": 66.0, \"text\": \"Saipov said nothing.\"}, {\"start\": 67.0, \"end\": 69.0, \"text\": \"He did not enter a plea.\"}, {\"start\": 72.0, \"end\": 76.0, \"text\": \"House Republicans gathered today\"}, {\"start\": 77.0, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"to unveil their new tax reform plan. It's called the\"}, {\"start\": 82.0, \"end\": 87.0, \"text\": \"Tax Cuts and Jobs Act. House speaker Paul Ryan\"}, {\"start\": 87.0, \"end\": 95.0, \"text\": \"said it is a much needed economic aid for the middle class.\"}, {\"start\": 96.0, \"end\": 101.0, \"text\": \"He says with this plan a typical family of four will\"}, {\"start\": 101.0, \"end\": 105.0, \"text\": \"save $1,182 dollars a year on their taxes.\"}, {\"start\": 106.0, \"end\": 112.0, \"text\": \"President Trump released a statement saying he supports the proposal.\"}, {\"start\": 113.0, \"end\": 118.0, \"text\": \"Here are a few details of the new plan. It permanently lowers\"}, {\"start\": 119.0, \"end\": 123.0, \"text\": \"the corporate tax rate to 20 percent.\"}, {\"start\": 124.0, \"end\": 129.0, \"text\": \"It reduces the number of individual tax brackets.\"}, {\"start\": 129.0, \"end\": 132.0, \"text\": \"It increases the child tax credit to\"}, {\"start\": 133.0, \"end\": 136.0, \"text\": \"$1600 dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 136.1, \"end\": 144.1, \"text\": \"It repeals the estate tax in 2024\"}, {\"start\": 144.1, \"end\": 146.1, \"text\": \"and it preserves property\"}, {\"start\": 147.0, \"end\": 148.0, \"text\": \"tax deductions.\"}, {\"start\": 152.0, \"end\": 156.0, \"text\": \"Former Trump campaign manager\"}, {\"start\": 157.0, \"end\": 158.0, \"text\": \"Paul Manafort\"}, {\"start\": 158.0, \"end\": 165.0, \"text\": \"was supposed to be in court today.\"}, {\"start\": 166.0, \"end\": 170.0, \"text\": \"His lawyer says he poses no flight risk and\"}, {\"start\": 170.0, \"end\": 174.0, \"text\": \"should not be held under house arrest.\"}, {\"start\": 175.0, \"end\": 179.0, \"text\": \"But the judge postponed the hearing because Manafort's\"}, {\"start\": 180.0, \"end\": 183.0, \"text\": \"attorney did not file the proper motions.\"}, {\"start\": 184.0, \"end\": 189.0, \"text\": \"Manafort is charged with several crimes\"}, {\"start\": 190.0, \"end\": 194.0, \"text\": \"including conspiracy against the United States.\"}, {\"start\": 195.0, \"end\": 202.0, \"text\": \"The charge came out of Special Prosecutor Robert Mueller's\"}, {\"start\": 202.0, \"end\": 206.0, \"text\": \"probe into Russia's meddling in the\"}, {\"start\": 207.0, \"end\": 212.0, \"text\": \"2016 presidential election. Manaforts's lawyer\"}, {\"start\": 212.0, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"says his 10 million dollar unsecured bond\"}, {\"start\": 218.0, \"end\": 222.0, \"text\": \"should be enough. But prosecutors say Manafort\"}, {\"start\": 222.0, \"end\": 227.0, \"text\": \"is a flight risk because of his history\"}, {\"start\": 227.0, \"end\": 231.0, \"text\": \"of deception.\"}, {\"start\": 232.0, \"end\": 236.0, \"text\": \"He also has millions of dollars in foreign bank accounts\"}, {\"start\": 237.0, \"end\": 242.0, \"text\": \"and three separate U.S. passports.\"}, {\"start\": 242.0, \"end\": 247.0, \"text\": \"The next hearing will be held on November 6th.\"}, {\"start\": 250.0, \"end\": 254.0, \"text\": \"A kidnapping victim made a daring escape\"}, {\"start\": 255.0, \"end\": 258.0, \"text\": \"from the trunk of her alleged captor's car\"}, {\"start\": 260.0, \"end\": 264.0, \"text\": \"and it was all caught on camera.\"}, {\"start\": 265.0, \"end\": 270.0, \"text\": \"Police in Alabama say the man broke into the woman's home on\"}, {\"start\": 270.0, \"end\": 276.0, \"text\": \"October 30th and kidnapped her.\"}, {\"start\": 276.0, \"end\": 281.0, \"text\": \"When he stopped at a gas station\"}, {\"start\": 281.0, \"end\": 286.0, \"text\": \"and went inside the woman who was in the\"}, {\"start\": 286.0, \"end\": 291.0, \"text\": \"trunk popped it open and ran for help. As she entered\"}, {\"start\": 291.0, \"end\": 296.0, \"text\": \"the gas station you can see the man flee.\"}, {\"start\": 297.0, \"end\": 300.0, \"text\": \"The man, Timothy Wyatt,\"}, {\"start\": 301.0, \"end\": 306.0, \"text\": \"was taken into police custody. He's being\"}, {\"start\": 306.0, \"end\": 311.0, \"text\": \"charged with robbery, kidnapping and\"}, {\"start\": 311.0, \"end\": 313.0, \"text\": \"domestic violence.\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 321.0, \"text\": \"Congratulations to the Houston Astros! The team and the city is\"}, {\"start\": 321.0, \"end\": 325.0, \"text\": \"celebrating its first World Series title\"}, {\"start\": 326.0, \"end\": 331.0, \"text\": \"in franchise history. Last night at Dodger\"}, {\"start\": 331.0, \"end\": 337.0, \"text\": \"Stadium the Astros beat the Dodgers 5-1 in Game 7.\"}, {\"start\": 337.0, \"end\": 341.0, \"text\": \"Centerfielder George Springer\"}, {\"start\": 342.0, \"end\": 350.0, \"text\": \"was named the World Series MVP.\"}, {\"start\": 350.0, \"end\": 354.0, \"text\": \"He hit a record tying five home runs\"}, {\"start\": 355.0, \"end\": 360.0, \"text\": \"and he became the first player to hit a home run\"}, {\"start\": 360.0, \"end\": 362.0, \"text\": \"in four straight World Series games.\"}, {\"start\": 362.0, \"end\": 366.0, \"text\": \"Again congratulations to the Houston Astros.\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 374.0, \"text\": \"Candy giant Hershey's just released its\"}, {\"start\": 374.0, \"end\": 378.0, \"text\": \"first new candy bar in 20 years.\"}, {\"start\": 378.0, \"end\": 382.0, \"text\": \"This is Hershey's Gold. Company officials\"}, {\"start\": 383.0, \"end\": 387.0, \"text\": \"describe the candy bar as a whole new\"}, {\"start\": 389.0, \"end\": 394.0, \"text\": \"flavor for the company. It mixes buttery\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 398.0, \"text\": \"sweet carmelized creme with\"}, {\"start\": 399.0, \"end\": 404.0, \"text\": \"crunchy bits of salt and peanuts. Hershey says the\"}, {\"start\": 404.0, \"end\": 409.0, \"text\": \"bar will go on sale nationwide next month.\"}, {\"start\": 413.0, \"end\": 416.0, \"text\": \"The latest Marvel Comics movie\"}, {\"start\": 417.0, \"end\": 422.0, \"text\": \"is set to hit theaters this weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 422.0, \"end\": 425.0, \"text\": \"One Hollywood executive says\"}, {\"start\": 426.0, \"end\": 432.0, \"text\": \"Thor Ragnarok\"}, {\"start\": 432.0, \"end\": 435.0, \"text\": \"will be a huge success at the box office.\"}, {\"start\": 436.0, \"end\": 441.0, \"text\": \"Actor Chris Hemsworth\"}, {\"start\": 441.0, \"end\": 448.0, \"text\": \"returns as the God of Thunder.\"}, {\"start\": 448.0, \"end\": 452.0, \"text\": \"The movie hasn't even hit theaters yet but it's already\"}, {\"start\": 452.0, \"end\": 456.0, \"text\": \"getting great reviews. Movie analysts say\"}, {\"start\": 457.0, \"end\": 465.0, \"text\": \"Thor Ragnarok is expected to haul in at least $120 million.\"}, {\"start\": 469.0, \"end\": 472.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today. I am Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 473.0, \"end\": 478.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Remember to like us on Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 478.0, \"end\": 481.0, \"text\": \"and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 482.024, \"end\": 489.024, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "obGTDNDP8nQ": {
    "video_id": "obGTDNDP8nQ",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.23.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180124",
    "duration": 500,
    "view_count": 982,
    "description": "1.23.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Multiple victims in Kentucky school shooting\n-Trump taxes foreign solar panels, washing machines\n-\"Talking stick\" helped end government shutdown\n-Earthquake strikes Alaska, Tsumani warning canceled\n-Kevin Spacey cost Netflix $39 million\n-Oscar nominations announced\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.88, \"end\": 9.26, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.26, \"end\": 11.02, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.14, \"end\": 12.98, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.98, \"end\": 15.36, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.44, \"end\": 23.1, \"text\": \"Police say a 15-year old student, armed with a handgun, walked into his high school in\"}, {\"start\": 23.1, \"end\": 26.9, \"text\": \"Marshall County, Kentucky and opened fire.\"}, {\"start\": 26.9, \"end\": 31.04, \"text\": \"Two teenagers are dead and 14 people are wounded.\"}, {\"start\": 31.04, \"end\": 38.76, \"text\": \"Police say the shooting started just before 8 AM.\"}, {\"start\": 38.76, \"end\": 45.52, \"text\": \"The first 9-1-1 call went out two minutes later and in seven minutes ATF, FBI and multiple\"}, {\"start\": 45.52, \"end\": 49.66, \"text\": \"police departments in the area were on the scene.\"}, {\"start\": 49.66, \"end\": 57.6, \"text\": \"The shooter was taken into custody and has been charged with murder and attempted murder.\"}, {\"start\": 58.96, \"end\": 68.22, \"text\": \"For the first time since becoming president, President Trump makes his first major trade\"}, {\"start\": 68.22, \"end\": 72.84, \"text\": \"action of 2018, which follows his campaign promise to get tough on America's trading partners.\"}, {\"start\": 72.84, \"end\": 80.42, \"text\": \"On Monday the Trump administration announced it is imposing taxes on imported solar panels\"}, {\"start\": 80.42, \"end\": 84.78, \"text\": \"and washing machines.\"}, {\"start\": 84.78, \"end\": 91.82, \"text\": \"A tax of 30 percent will be applied to imported solar panels, most of which come from China.\"}, {\"start\": 91.82, \"end\": 96.5, \"text\": \"Taxes will begin at 20 percent on large residential washing machines.\"}, {\"start\": 96.5, \"end\": 107.72, \"text\": \"The decision comes after the independent US International Trade Commission determined\"}, {\"start\": 107.72, \"end\": 113.9, \"text\": \"imports of solar panels and washers had hurt American companies.\"}, {\"start\": 115.56, \"end\": 131.82, \"text\": \"Maine Senator Susan Collins is showing the \\\"talking stick\\\" that apparently played a role\"}, {\"start\": 131.82, \"end\": 133.9, \"text\": \"in ending the government shutdown.\"}, {\"start\": 133.9, \"end\": 148.82, \"text\": \"The stick was used during bipartisan talks in her office to make sure that only the person\"}, {\"start\": 148.82, \"end\": 152.14, \"text\": \"holding the stick speaks.\"}, {\"start\": 152.14, \"end\": 158.76, \"text\": \"Collins says the talking stick has its roots in Africa and it is used to help control the\"}, {\"start\": 158.76, \"end\": 162.66, \"text\": \"debate in a meeting, particularly when there is a large group of people who all want to\"}, {\"start\": 162.66, \"end\": 165.22, \"text\": \"talk.\"}, {\"start\": 165.22, \"end\": 170.48, \"text\": \"Collins says the stick made sure everybody's voice got heard.\"}, {\"start\": 170.48, \"end\": 176.0, \"text\": \"She would pick up the stick and take it to the person who wanted to talk.\"}, {\"start\": 176.0, \"end\": 182.86, \"text\": \"Collins said on one occasion, the stick was tossed across the room but it missed the person\"}, {\"start\": 182.86, \"end\": 185.54, \"text\": \"and damaged a shelf instead.\"}, {\"start\": 185.54, \"end\": 194.0, \"text\": \"One Republican senator said other than that one mistake, the stick apparently worked.\"}, {\"start\": 195.46, \"end\": 204.74, \"text\": \"A 7.9 magnitude earthquake shook Alaska a little after midnight Alaska time.\"}, {\"start\": 204.74, \"end\": 210.52, \"text\": \"It struck about 175 miles offshore of Kodiak, Alaska.\"}, {\"start\": 210.52, \"end\": 220.32, \"text\": \"The quake was felt by boaters in the Gulf of Alaska and residents in Anchorage.\"}, {\"start\": 220.32, \"end\": 226.84, \"text\": \"The magnitude of the quake triggered a tsunami warning.\"}, {\"start\": 226.84, \"end\": 234.88, \"text\": \"Police warned residents to move to high ground to stay safe from waters that could rise quickly.\"}, {\"start\": 234.88, \"end\": 239.84, \"text\": \"But the Tsunami Warning Center eventually canceled all warnings in Alaska and Canada\"}, {\"start\": 239.84, \"end\": 248.7, \"text\": \"as well as the tsunami watch for the West Coast and Hawaii.\"}, {\"start\": 250.52, \"end\": 254.58, \"text\": \"Kevin Spacey apparently cost Netflix $39 million.\"}, {\"start\": 254.58, \"end\": 258.18, \"text\": \"A source tells CNN that the charge is entirely from costs associated from ending the show\"}, {\"start\": 258.18, \"end\": 268.48, \"text\": \"\\\"House of Cards\\\" and deciding not to proceed with the release of the movie \\\"Gore.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 268.48, \"end\": 273.74, \"text\": \"Both of those projects starred Spacey.\"}, {\"start\": 273.74, \"end\": 280.88, \"text\": \"The actor was accused of sexual misconduct by several people late last year.\"}, {\"start\": 280.88, \"end\": 285.62, \"text\": \"But Spacey is not the only Netflix star to be accused of sexual harassment or misconduct.\"}, {\"start\": 285.62, \"end\": 289.4, \"text\": \"Netflix has also canceled plans for another stand up special from comedian Louis CK because\"}, {\"start\": 289.4, \"end\": 295.0, \"text\": \"of sexual misconduct allegations.\"}, {\"start\": 295.0, \"end\": 309.6, \"text\": \"And actor Danny Masterson was written out of \\\"The Ranch\\\" amid rape allegations.\"}, {\"start\": 311.64, \"end\": 319.92, \"text\": \"The nominees for the 90th Academy Awards were announced Tuesday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 319.92, \"end\": 322.16, \"text\": \"Here's a look at a couple of the contenders:\"}, {\"start\": 322.16, \"end\": 333.28, \"text\": \"\\\"The Shape of Water\\\" leads this year's Oscar field with 13 nominees, including best picture.\"}, {\"start\": 333.28, \"end\": 347.5, \"text\": \"Golden Globe and SAG winner Gary Oldman's portrayal of Winston Churchill has led to\"}, {\"start\": 347.5, \"end\": 350.42, \"text\": \"a lead actor nomination in \\\"Darkest Hour.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 350.42, \"end\": 359.88, \"text\": \"Frances McDormand is also a Golden Globe and SAG winner and she was nominated in the lead\"}, {\"start\": 359.88, \"end\": 365.02, \"text\": \"actress category for her role in \\\"Three Billboards.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 365.02, \"end\": 371.38, \"text\": \"Greta Gerwig made Oscar history by becoming the first woman nominated for best director\"}, {\"start\": 371.38, \"end\": 375.94, \"text\": \"in her debut film \\\"Lady Bird.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 375.94, \"end\": 396.04, \"text\": \"\\\"Call Me By Your Name\\\" star Timothee Chalamet is the youngest actor nominee since Mickey\"}, {\"start\": 396.04, \"end\": 397.84, \"text\": \"Rooney in 1944.\"}, {\"start\": 397.84, \"end\": 402.4, \"text\": \"And 88-year-old Christopher Plummer is the oldest nominee in Oscar history.\"}, {\"start\": 402.4, \"end\": 421.56, \"text\": \"He is up for best supporting actor for his performance as J. Paul Getty in \\\"All The Money\"}, {\"start\": 421.56, \"end\": 426.6, \"text\": \"in the World.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 426.6, \"end\": 437.24, \"text\": \"Jordan Peele is the first black director to receive three nominations for \\\"Get Out\\\" -- best\"}, {\"start\": 437.24, \"end\": 444.68, \"text\": \"picture, best director and best original screenplay.\"}, {\"start\": 444.68, \"end\": 458.12, \"text\": \"And \\\"Mudbound\\\" star Mary J. Blige is the first person nominated for best actress and best\"}, {\"start\": 458.12, \"end\": 460.94, \"text\": \"original song in the same year.\"}, {\"start\": 460.94, \"end\": 469.06, \"text\": \"The 90th Academy Awards will be hosted by Jimmy Kimmel in Hollywood on Sunday, March 4th.\"}, {\"start\": 471.28, \"end\": 473.78, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 473.96, \"end\": 475.52, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 475.52, \"end\": 477.92, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 477.92, \"end\": 483.18, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 483.18, \"end\": 490.52, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "xZIfn4aIJ6o": {
    "video_id": "xZIfn4aIJ6o",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.13.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171014",
    "duration": 483,
    "view_count": 1030,
    "description": "October 13, 2017\nSign1News delivers news for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).\n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-DEATH TOLL RISING IN CALIFORNIA WILDFIRES\n-FLAMES INSIDE HOLLOW TREE\n-FIREFIGHTERS NEED A BREAK\n-TRUMP WANTS TO SCRAP IRAN DEAL\n-“BREAKING BAD” HOUSE BOMBARDED WITH PIZZA\n-DRINKING ENOUGH WATER?\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE\nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrounds from notable organizations such as GALLAUDET UNIVERSITY",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 10.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.0, \"end\": 14.0, \"text\": \"I am Jethro Wooddall. And here\"}, {\"start\": 15.0, \"end\": 18.0, \"text\": \"are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 20.0, \"end\": 25.0, \"text\": \"Yesterday we reported 23 people had died in the California\"}, {\"start\": 25.0, \"end\": 29.0, \"text\": \"wildfires. Sadly, that number has now risen to 31 people.\"}, {\"start\": 29.0, \"end\": 34.0, \"text\": \"Fire officials say they cannot stress this message enough: Get out\"}, {\"start\": 34.0, \"end\": 39.0, \"text\": \"now or you're on your own! This disaster has\"}, {\"start\": 39.0, \"end\": 44.0, \"text\": \"become the deadliest week of wildfires in California's\"}, {\"start\": 44.0, \"end\": 48.0, \"text\": \"history. Hundreds of people cannot be\"}, {\"start\": 48.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"located by their family and friends. Authorities\"}, {\"start\": 53.0, \"end\": 58.0, \"text\": \"must wait for houses to cool before they can go inside to\"}, {\"start\": 58.0, \"end\": 64.0, \"text\": \"search for the missing. And the weather is not helping.\"}, {\"start\": 64.0, \"end\": 70.0, \"text\": \"A red flag warning has been issued in northern California.\"}, {\"start\": 70.0, \"end\": 75.0, \"text\": \"Winds are expected to strengthen and there's no rain in the forecast --\"}, {\"start\": 75.0, \"end\": 80.0, \"text\": \"which means the fire will continue to spread. One official says the\"}, {\"start\": 80.0, \"end\": 84.0, \"text\": \"misery and heartbreak aren't going to end\"}, {\"start\": 84.0, \"end\": 87.0, \"text\": \"anytime soon.\"}, {\"start\": 90.0, \"end\": 95.0, \"text\": \"Incredible images are pouring out of California showing\"}, {\"start\": 95.0, \"end\": 99.0, \"text\": \"the wildfire consuming acres of homes, land and trees.\"}, {\"start\": 99.0, \"end\": 103.0, \"text\": \"On Monday a man in Sonoma County was driving\"}, {\"start\": 103.0, \"end\": 108.0, \"text\": \"around trying to find an escape route when he came across this\"}, {\"start\": 109.0, \"end\": 113.0, \"text\": \"unusual sight -- a tree burning from the\"}, {\"start\": 114.0, \"end\": 118.0, \"text\": \"inside out. You can see the eerie glow\"}, {\"start\": 119.0, \"end\": 123.0, \"text\": \"peeking out through the holes in the tree's bark.\"}, {\"start\": 125.0, \"end\": 130.0, \"text\": \"Firefighters are exhausted. These are pictures of\"}, {\"start\": 130.0, \"end\": 133.0, \"text\": \"firefighters trying to get some rest\"}, {\"start\": 134.0, \"end\": 139.0, \"text\": \"before going back out to fight the fires again.\"}, {\"start\": 139.0, \"end\": 143.0, \"text\": \"They say this is the worst fire they have ever\"}, {\"start\": 144.0, \"end\": 148.0, \"text\": \"seen. Roughly 500 to 800\"}, {\"start\": 148.0, \"end\": 153.0, \"text\": \"firefighters are doing what they can to\"}, {\"start\": 153.0, \"end\": 157.0, \"text\": \"extinguish the flames. They are working extended shifts\"}, {\"start\": 158.0, \"end\": 162.0, \"text\": \"and trying to sleep wherever and whenever they can.\"}, {\"start\": 165.0, \"end\": 170.0, \"text\": \"In 2015 the U.S. and other powerful countries\"}, {\"start\": 171.0, \"end\": 175.0, \"text\": \"came to an agreement -- they would ease\"}, {\"start\": 175.0, \"end\": 180.0, \"text\": \"sanctions on Iran if they were allowed to monitor\"}, {\"start\": 180.0, \"end\": 185.0, \"text\": \"Iran's nuclear development activities. According to President\"}, {\"start\": 185.0, \"end\": 189.0, \"text\": \"Trump that deal also included a cash\"}, {\"start\": 189.0, \"end\": 194.0, \"text\": \"payment of $1.7 billion dollars\"}, {\"start\": 195.0, \"end\": 199.0, \"text\": \"approved by President Obama. Now President\"}, {\"start\": 199.0, \"end\": 205.0, \"text\": \"Trump says Iran is not living up to the deal.\"}, {\"start\": 205.0, \"end\": 210.0, \"text\": \"He says in the original nuclear deal, Iran was supposed to\"}, {\"start\": 210.0, \"end\": 216.0, \"text\": \"contribute to peace and security around the world.\"}, {\"start\": 216.0, \"end\": 221.0, \"text\": \"But now he believes Iran is building nuclear\"}, {\"start\": 221.0, \"end\": 225.0, \"text\": \"weapons to cause conflict,\"}, {\"start\": 225.0, \"end\": 230.0, \"text\": \"terror and turmoil. He wants to\"}, {\"start\": 230.0, \"end\": 236.0, \"text\": \"scrap the original deal with Iran and implement a new aggressive strategy.\"}, {\"start\": 236.0, \"end\": 241.0, \"text\": \"Congress has 60 days to decide whether or\"}, {\"start\": 241.0, \"end\": 245.0, \"text\": \"not to agree. But some leaders in Washington\"}, {\"start\": 245.0, \"end\": 250.0, \"text\": \"D.C. think this is a bad idea.\"}, {\"start\": 250.0, \"end\": 254.0, \"text\": \"They say if President Trump scraps the deal,\"}, {\"start\": 255.0, \"end\": 259.0, \"text\": \"it will threaten America's security. They say the\"}, {\"start\": 259.0, \"end\": 264.0, \"text\": \"president is ignoring the advice of\"}, {\"start\": 264.0, \"end\": 269.0, \"text\": \"nuclear scientists, national\"}, {\"start\": 270.0, \"end\": 275.0, \"text\": \"security experts, generals and his own cabinet -- including\"}, {\"start\": 275.0, \"end\": 280.0, \"text\": \"the Secretary of Defense and the Secretary of State.\"}, {\"start\": 283.024, \"end\": 286.024, \"text\": \"Were you a fan of the TV show\"}, {\"start\": 287.0, \"end\": 291.0, \"text\": \"\\\"Breaking Bad?\\\" Remember the\"}, {\"start\": 292.0, \"end\": 296.0, \"text\": \"scene where Walter threw a pizza\"}, {\"start\": 296.0, \"end\": 301.0, \"text\": \"on the roof of the house?\"}, {\"start\": 301.5, \"end\": 305.5, \"text\": \"The real home from the show is in\"}, {\"start\": 306.0, \"end\": 311.0, \"text\": \"Albuquerque, New Mexico and the owners\"}, {\"start\": 311.0, \"end\": 316.0, \"text\": \"say they are tired of fans\"}, {\"start\": 316.0, \"end\": 322.0, \"text\": \"parking in their driveway, snapping pictures and\"}, {\"start\": 322.0, \"end\": 327.0, \"text\": \"even throwing pizzas on the roof!\"}, {\"start\": 327.0, \"end\": 332.0, \"text\": \"The owners are now putting up a 6-foot\"}, {\"start\": 332.0, \"end\": 336.0, \"text\": \"fence around the property, cameras,\"}, {\"start\": 336.001, \"end\": 338.001, \"text\": \"signs and cones\"}, {\"start\": 338.1, \"end\": 341.1, \"text\": \"to keep gawkers at a distance.\"}, {\"start\": 343.001, \"end\": 347.001, \"text\": \"If you're feeling tired and moody during the day,\"}, {\"start\": 347.1, \"end\": 351.1, \"text\": \"it may be because you're not drinking enough water.\"}, {\"start\": 351.1, \"end\": 355.1, \"text\": \"Drinking at least eight 8-ounce glasses of water a day\"}, {\"start\": 356.0, \"end\": 361.0, \"text\": \"helps regulate the body temperature,\"}, {\"start\": 361.0, \"end\": 365.0, \"text\": \"it helps deliver nutrients\"}, {\"start\": 366.0, \"end\": 370.0, \"text\": \"to your cells, protects sensitive\"}, {\"start\": 370.0, \"end\": 375.0, \"text\": \"tissue and hydrates the\"}, {\"start\": 375.0, \"end\": 380.0, \"text\": \"skin. Water helps our kidneys and\"}, {\"start\": 381.0, \"end\": 386.0, \"text\": \"liver get rid of toxins in our bodies.\"}, {\"start\": 386.0, \"end\": 394.0, \"text\": \"And most importantly it keeps us hydrated.\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 397.0, \"text\": \"Water makes up about 60 percent of our body\"}, {\"start\": 397.0, \"end\": 401.0, \"text\": \"weight. Most people\"}, {\"start\": 401.0, \"end\": 406.0, \"text\": \"can live without food for weeks.\"}, {\"start\": 406.0, \"end\": 411.0, \"text\": \"But dehydration can kill within days or even hours --\"}, {\"start\": 411.0, \"end\": 416.0, \"text\": \"depending on the temperature and the environment.\"}, {\"start\": 418.001, \"end\": 420.001, \"text\": \"The amount of water your\"}, {\"start\": 420.1, \"end\": 423.1, \"text\": \"body needs each day may differ from someone else's.\"}, {\"start\": 423.1, \"end\": 427.1, \"text\": \"The National academies of sciences, engineering and medicine\"}, {\"start\": 427.124, \"end\": 429.124, \"text\": \"say that the average male should drink\"}, {\"start\": 429.2, \"end\": 434.2, \"text\": \"3.7 liters of fluid every day. It's about\"}, {\"start\": 435.0, \"end\": 439.0, \"text\": \"2.7 liters for women. You can also get water from\"}, {\"start\": 439.0, \"end\": 444.0, \"text\": \"fruits and vegetables such as lettuce,\"}, {\"start\": 444.0, \"end\": 452.0, \"text\": \"cucumbers, watermelon and grapes.\"}, {\"start\": 455.0, \"end\": 460.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for the day. I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 460.0, \"end\": 464.0, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News. Remember to \\\"Like\\\" us on Facebook\"}, {\"start\": 464.0, \"end\": 468.0, \"text\": \"and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 468.024, \"end\": 476.024, \"text\": \"Sign1 News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "eFh6kDzJQ2M": {
    "video_id": "eFh6kDzJQ2M",
    "title": "Students walk out of school across the country (ASL - 2.21.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180222",
    "duration": 80,
    "view_count": 61,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.54, \"end\": 10.88, \"text\": \"Thousands of students across the country walked out of their schools to protest gun laws and\"}, {\"start\": 10.88, \"end\": 12.68, \"text\": \"demand school safety.\"}, {\"start\": 12.68, \"end\": 18.45, \"text\": \"These are images from Tallahassee, Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 18.45, \"end\": 25.06, \"text\": \"Students stormed the state Capitol rotunda, demanding to be heard.\"}, {\"start\": 25.06, \"end\": 29.88, \"text\": \"Some students said they were turned away from legislators' offices.\"}, {\"start\": 29.88, \"end\": 34.199, \"text\": \"They were told meetings were \\\"by appointment\\\" only.\"}, {\"start\": 34.2, \"end\": 37.96, \"text\": \"That's when students started shouting \\\"Vote them out!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 37.96, \"end\": 46.499, \"text\": \"This was the scene in Washington, DC as hundreds of teens walked out of their schools in support\"}, {\"start\": 46.499, \"end\": 51.35, \"text\": \"of the students at Marjory Stoneman Douglas high school.\"}, {\"start\": 51.35, \"end\": 60.36, \"text\": \"They boarded a train at Union Station and marched to the Capitol to call for action\"}, {\"start\": 60.36, \"end\": 64.52, \"text\": \"on gun violence.\"}, {\"start\": 64.52, \"end\": 71.5, \"text\": \"Students at Coral Springs high school in Florida walked out and sent a message of peace by\"}, {\"start\": 71.5, \"end\": 78.82, \"text\": \"forming a giant heart in the middle of the football field.\"}]"
  },
  "jaXvjJyXW6g": {
    "video_id": "jaXvjJyXW6g",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.2.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180303",
    "duration": 674,
    "view_count": 1260,
    "description": "3.2.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-“Bomb cyclone” is life or death situation\n-Two dead in shooting at C. Michigan University\n-Billy Graham laid to rest\n-Trump and Alec Baldwin square off in twitter duel\n-Amazing video of python VS deer\n-Trading in your car\n-Meghan and Harry invite public to royal wedding\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and informa",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.6, \"end\": 9.74, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.74, \"end\": 11.24, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.26, \"end\": 13.28, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 13.28, \"end\": 16.58, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.66, \"end\": 27.84, \"text\": \"The National Weather Service is calling the storm slamming the East Coast this weekend\"}, {\"start\": 27.84, \"end\": 30.96, \"text\": \"a \\\"life and death\\\" situation.\"}, {\"start\": 30.96, \"end\": 42.24, \"text\": \"Forecasters say the storm has already reached bomb cyclone status, which happens when there\"}, {\"start\": 42.24, \"end\": 47.86, \"text\": \"is a rapid, dramatic drop in atmospheric pressure.\"}, {\"start\": 47.86, \"end\": 56.62, \"text\": \"That will cause drenching rain, hurricane-strength gusts of wind and coastal flooding.\"}, {\"start\": 56.7, \"end\": 71.96, \"text\": \"Roughly 80 million people are the storm's path with 22 million under coastal flood warnings.\"}, {\"start\": 71.96, \"end\": 82.56, \"text\": \"Authorities warn residents in the most populated coastal areas the worst is yet to come.\"}, {\"start\": 82.56, \"end\": 93.49, \"text\": \"Parts of Massachusetts and New York State are expected to get hit the hardest.\"}, {\"start\": 93.49, \"end\": 97.78, \"text\": \"People living on the coast are being asked to be prepared to evacuate.\"}, {\"start\": 97.78, \"end\": 105.48, \"text\": \"The storm is also impacting travel, forcing the cancellation of more than 2,000 flights.\"}, {\"start\": 108.86, \"end\": 115.2, \"text\": \"Two people are dead after a shooting inside a Central Michigan University dormitory Friday\"}, {\"start\": 115.2, \"end\": 117.159, \"text\": \"morning.\"}, {\"start\": 117.159, \"end\": 128.759, \"text\": \"Police say 19-year-old James Eric Davis, Junior is responsible.\"}, {\"start\": 128.759, \"end\": 134.36, \"text\": \"Authorities say the shooting happended around 8:30am on the fourth floor of Campbell Hall\"}, {\"start\": 134.36, \"end\": 137.34, \"text\": \"Dormitory.\"}, {\"start\": 137.34, \"end\": 146.38, \"text\": \"There are several reports that the two people killed were Davis' parents who came to pick\"}, {\"start\": 146.38, \"end\": 152.3, \"text\": \"him up for spring break.\"}, {\"start\": 152.3, \"end\": 158.24, \"text\": \"Students say they received a robo call Friday morning from the university alerting them\"}, {\"start\": 158.24, \"end\": 161.2, \"text\": \"about the shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 163.84, \"end\": 173.52, \"text\": \"The Reverend Billy Graham was laid to rest today at a private funeral service in Charlotte, NC.\"}, {\"start\": 173.7, \"end\": 183.12, \"text\": \"Hundreds of people attended the funeral including President Trump, First Lady Melania Trump\"}, {\"start\": 183.12, \"end\": 188.96, \"text\": \"and former presidents George W. Bush and Bill Clinton.\"}, {\"start\": 188.96, \"end\": 195.46, \"text\": \"The funeral capped off a week of tributes and honors.\"}, {\"start\": 195.46, \"end\": 207.68, \"text\": \"On Saturday mourners lined the roadways between Asheville and Charlotte for a glimpse of the\"}, {\"start\": 207.68, \"end\": 213.5, \"text\": \"motorcade carrying Graham's body.\"}, {\"start\": 213.5, \"end\": 220.78, \"text\": \"On Monday and Tuesday his body lay in repose in his childhood home.\"}, {\"start\": 220.78, \"end\": 234.34, \"text\": \"On Wednesday and Thursday Graham lay in honor inside the US Capitol rotunda, a rare honor.\"}, {\"start\": 234.34, \"end\": 241.94, \"text\": \"And now his final resting place will be buried next to his wife, Ruth, at the Billy Graham\"}, {\"start\": 241.94, \"end\": 244.64, \"text\": \"Library prayer garden in Charlotte.\"}, {\"start\": 248.18, \"end\": 263.3, \"text\": \"President Trump apparently woke up Friday morning with actor Alec Baldwin on his mind.\"}, {\"start\": 263.3, \"end\": 276.82, \"text\": \"He tweeted: \\\"Alex Baldwin, who's dieing mediocre career was saved by his impersonation of me\"}, {\"start\": 276.82, \"end\": 290.86, \"text\": \"on SNL, now says playing D-J-T was agony for him.\"}, {\"start\": 290.86, \"end\": 301.28, \"text\": \"Alex, it was also agony for those who were forced to watch.\"}, {\"start\": 301.32, \"end\": 304.12, \"text\": \"You were terrible.\"}, {\"start\": 304.12, \"end\": 314.64, \"text\": \"Bring back Darrell Hammond, much funnier and a far greater talent!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 314.64, \"end\": 323.52, \"text\": \"Trump later deleted his original tweet and then retweeted it with the correct spelling\"}, {\"start\": 323.52, \"end\": 334.44, \"text\": \"of Alec's name and the word \\\"dying.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 334.44, \"end\": 351.1, \"text\": \"Baldwin then hit right back, tweeting: \\\"Agony though it may be, I'd like to hang in there\"}, {\"start\": 351.1, \"end\": 367.04, \"text\": \"for the impeachment hearings, the resignation speech, the farewell helicopter ride to Mar-a-Lago.\"}, {\"start\": 367.04, \"end\": 368.1, \"text\": \"You know.\"}, {\"start\": 368.34, \"end\": 372.26, \"text\": \"The good stuff that we've all been waiting for.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 372.28, \"end\": 380.2, \"text\": \"He finished by saying: \\\"And Mr. President please ask your wife to stop calling me for\"}, {\"start\": 380.2, \"end\": 384.06, \"text\": \"SNL tickets.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 387.44, \"end\": 392.74, \"text\": \"We want to warn you the following images are a little disturbing.\"}, {\"start\": 392.74, \"end\": 394.84, \"text\": \"But they are also rather fascinating.\"}, {\"start\": 394.84, \"end\": 413.34, \"text\": \"Biologists in Florida released images of a Burmese python trying to swallow a deer whole!\"}, {\"start\": 413.34, \"end\": 422.72, \"text\": \"The discovery was made in Collier-Seminole State Park in April 2015.\"}, {\"start\": 422.72, \"end\": 443.96, \"text\": \"Pythons have been known to swallow large animals but what stunned scientists is the predator-to-prey ratio.\"}, {\"start\": 443.96, \"end\": 455.5, \"text\": \"The 11-foot python weighed 31.5 pounds; the deer was 35 pounds, nearly 5 pounds heavier\"}, {\"start\": 455.5, \"end\": 456.82, \"text\": \"than the python.\"}, {\"start\": 456.82, \"end\": 466.3, \"text\": \"They believe it to be the largest predator-to-prey ratio ever documented for a Burmese python.\"}, {\"start\": 466.3, \"end\": 476.4, \"text\": \"Scientists eventually had to euthanize the python because trying to digest an animal\"}, {\"start\": 476.4, \"end\": 480.04, \"text\": \"of that size caused it severe stress.\"}, {\"start\": 483.24, \"end\": 487.34, \"text\": \"If you're shopping for new car this year, chances are you will be trading in your old\"}, {\"start\": 487.34, \"end\": 492.1, \"text\": \"one and you want to make sure you're getting the most money from the trade-in.\"}, {\"start\": 492.1, \"end\": 494.88, \"text\": \"Here are a few tips to help you.\"}, {\"start\": 494.88, \"end\": 506.86, \"text\": \"According to car buying advisor Edmunds, start by getting more than one offer.\"}, {\"start\": 506.86, \"end\": 526.24, \"text\": \"First get an online appraisal then get trade-in quotes from several dealerships.\"}, {\"start\": 526.24, \"end\": 530.46, \"text\": \"This will give you a better understanding of your vehicle's actual value.\"}, {\"start\": 530.46, \"end\": 534.22, \"text\": \"Keep an eye on the timing of your trade-in.\"}, {\"start\": 534.22, \"end\": 539.84, \"text\": \"You want to do it before you renew your registration.\"}, {\"start\": 539.84, \"end\": 549.92, \"text\": \"And if you lease, trade it in before your upcoming payment.\"}, {\"start\": 549.92, \"end\": 556.8, \"text\": \"But hold off on replacing tires or doing repairs.\"}, {\"start\": 556.8, \"end\": 564.72, \"text\": \"Chances are you're not going to get a better trade-in value by taking care of those issues\"}, {\"start\": 564.72, \"end\": 565.98, \"text\": \"yourself.\"}, {\"start\": 565.98, \"end\": 568.18, \"text\": \"Check your insurance claims.\"}, {\"start\": 568.18, \"end\": 573.94, \"text\": \"If you had any accidents, it will most likely drop the value of the vehicle.\"}, {\"start\": 573.94, \"end\": 580.04, \"text\": \"And make sure you have all your service records and receipts.\"}, {\"start\": 580.04, \"end\": 591.9, \"text\": \"Dealerships see you as a responsible car owner who has a well-maintained vehicle which is\"}, {\"start\": 591.9, \"end\": 593.62, \"text\": \"usually more valuable.\"}, {\"start\": 597.34, \"end\": 608.36, \"text\": \"Kensington Palace announced Friday Prince Harry and Meghan Markle have invited more\"}, {\"start\": 608.36, \"end\": 617.5, \"text\": \"than 2,600 people onto the grounds of Windsor Castle to share in the royal wedding festivities.\"}, {\"start\": 617.5, \"end\": 625.02, \"text\": \"Among those invited are local school children, charity workers and members of the public.\"}, {\"start\": 625.02, \"end\": 633.74, \"text\": \"The invitees will be able to watch the arrivals of the bride and groom at St. George's Chapel,\"}, {\"start\": 633.74, \"end\": 637.14, \"text\": \"where the ceremony takes place on May 19th.\"}, {\"start\": 637.14, \"end\": 646.32, \"text\": \"They will also see the newlyweds depart the castle on a carriage procession through the\"}, {\"start\": 646.32, \"end\": 648.58, \"text\": \"town of Windsor.\"}, {\"start\": 651.22, \"end\": 654.32, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 654.36, \"end\": 655.88, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 655.88, \"end\": 657.56, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 657.56, \"end\": 662.26, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 662.28, \"end\": 666.9, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "Llgrxnk6LCE": {
    "video_id": "Llgrxnk6LCE",
    "title": "Jennifer Lopez speaking out on being sexually harassed (ASL - 3.16.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180316",
    "duration": 44,
    "view_count": 523,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.64, \"end\": 16.66, \"text\": \"Jennifer Lopez is sharing her experience of being sexually harassed in Hollywood.\"}, {\"start\": 16.66, \"end\": 23.92, \"text\": \"In an interview with \\\"Harper's Bazaar\\\" the actress, singer and producer detailed an experience\"}, {\"start\": 23.92, \"end\": 26.08, \"text\": \"she had very early in her career.\"}, {\"start\": 26.08, \"end\": 31.72, \"text\": \"She said the director of one of her first movies told her to take off her shirt and\"}, {\"start\": 31.72, \"end\": 33.26, \"text\": \"show her breasts.\"}, {\"start\": 33.26, \"end\": 37.12, \"text\": \"She says she was terrified but ultimately refused to remove her shirt.\"}, {\"start\": 37.12, \"end\": 42.78, \"text\": \"Lopez never revealed the director's name in the interview.\"}]"
  },
  "01DtCzgzaUU": {
    "video_id": "01DtCzgzaUU",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.27.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180228",
    "duration": 480,
    "view_count": 1142,
    "description": "2.27.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-11 ill after opening suspicious letter\n-Trump son-in-law loses \"Top Secret\" clearance\n-Trump hires campaign chief for 2020 presidential run\n-Virginia and New York wooing Delta\n-1 in 7 teens are sexting \n-E-cigarettes and heart attacks\n-Suspect caught hiding drugs in police station ceiling\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-l",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.0, \"end\": 8.96, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.96, \"end\": 11.28, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.28, \"end\": 12.44, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 12.44, \"end\": 15.68, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.28, \"end\": 30.8, \"text\": \"Fire officials say 11 people became ill after coming in contact with a suspicious letter\"}, {\"start\": 30.8, \"end\": 39.24, \"text\": \"at Joint Base Myer-Henderson Hall in Arlington, Virginia.\"}, {\"start\": 39.24, \"end\": 43.8, \"text\": \"This is a local military base where Army and Marine Corps soldiers live and work.\"}, {\"start\": 43.8, \"end\": 49.96, \"text\": \"Officials say when the letter was opened several people exhibited symptoms of burning hands\"}, {\"start\": 50.0, \"end\": 54.48, \"text\": \"and face and one person's nose started bleeding.\"}, {\"start\": 54.48, \"end\": 60.36, \"text\": \"Three people were transported to the hospital where they are listed in stable condition.\"}, {\"start\": 60.36, \"end\": 64.2, \"text\": \"It is unclear who opened the letter.\"}, {\"start\": 64.2, \"end\": 68.56, \"text\": \"Federal law enforcement agents launched an immediate investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 71.16, \"end\": 82.08, \"text\": \"On February 16th White House Chief of Staff John Kelly issued a memo that stated temporary\"}, {\"start\": 82.08, \"end\": 89.08, \"text\": \"security clearances for certain White House aides be downgraded or discontinued,\"}, {\"start\": 89.08, \"end\": 91.8, \"text\": \"limting their access to the nation's secrets.\"}, {\"start\": 91.81, \"end\": 104.01, \"text\": \"One of those aides is President Trump's son-in-law Jared Kushner, who serves as senior advisor.\"}, {\"start\": 104.01, \"end\": 110.48, \"text\": \"Today Kushner was stripped of his \\\"top-secret\\\" access to the nation secrets, downgraded to\"}, {\"start\": 110.48, \"end\": 113.88, \"text\": \"classification for less sensitive material.\"}, {\"start\": 113.88, \"end\": 120.68, \"text\": \"Sources say Kushner is accepting the decision and will not ask for special permission or\"}, {\"start\": 120.68, \"end\": 123.68, \"text\": \"clearance from the president.\"}, {\"start\": 125.48, \"end\": 132.2, \"text\": \"The next presidential election is more than two-and-a-half years away and it's highly\"}, {\"start\": 132.2, \"end\": 139.4, \"text\": \"unusual for a president to hire a campaign manager so far before the election.\"}, {\"start\": 139.4, \"end\": 145.12, \"text\": \"But President Trump has already hired his campaign chief for 2020.\"}, {\"start\": 145.12, \"end\": 151.4, \"text\": \"Sources tell CNN Brad Parscale, Trump's digital media director during the 2016 presidential\"}, {\"start\": 151.4, \"end\": 154.2, \"text\": \"race, will run his 2020 campaign.\"}, {\"start\": 154.2, \"end\": 159.48, \"text\": \"Parscale had no political experience before he joined the first Trump campaign but he\"}, {\"start\": 159.48, \"end\": 164.28, \"text\": \"played a big role behind the scenes.\"}, {\"start\": 164.28, \"end\": 174.64, \"text\": \"Parscale has been active in Trump's political operation \\\"America First\\\" since Trump was elected.\"}, {\"start\": 176.56, \"end\": 185.68, \"text\": \"Last week, Delta Airlines joined several other companies by announcing it would no longer\"}, {\"start\": 185.68, \"end\": 190.8, \"text\": \"offer NRA members discounts following the school shooting in Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 190.8, \"end\": 197.76, \"text\": \"As a result, Georgia Republicans are threatening to kill part of a new bill that would eliminate\"}, {\"start\": 197.76, \"end\": 203.44, \"text\": \"a state tax for jet fuel.\"}, {\"start\": 203.44, \"end\": 215.44, \"text\": \"Georgia's Lt. Gov. Casey Cagle tweeted: \\\"I will kill any tax legislation that benefits\"}, {\"start\": 215.44, \"end\": 221.96, \"text\": \"Delta unless the company changes its position and fully reinstates its relationship with\"}, {\"start\": 221.96, \"end\": 225.76, \"text\": \"the NRA.\"}, {\"start\": 225.76, \"end\": 236.12, \"text\": \"Corporations cannot attack conservatives and expect us not to fight back.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 236.12, \"end\": 242.28, \"text\": \"Immediately lawmakers in Virginia and New York sent messages inviting Delta to move\"}, {\"start\": 242.32, \"end\": 247.16, \"text\": \"its headquarters to their states.\"}, {\"start\": 247.16, \"end\": 260.28, \"text\": \"On Twitter, Virginia's governor Ralph Northam wrote: \\\"Virginia is for lovers and airline hubs.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 260.28, \"end\": 262.6, \"text\": \"You're welcome here anytime.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 262.6, \"end\": 273.84, \"text\": \"New York Lt. Governor Kathy Hochul tweeted: \\\"Delta, as one of your most frequent flyers,\"}, {\"start\": 273.84, \"end\": 277.88, \"text\": \"know that the NYLG admires your principled stance.\"}, {\"start\": 277.88, \"end\": 281.96, \"text\": \"Move HQ to where you're appreciated.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 283.68, \"end\": 290.56, \"text\": \"A new study shows a rise in the number of teens either sending or receiving sexually\"}, {\"start\": 290.58, \"end\": 293.26, \"text\": \"explicit texts.\"}, {\"start\": 293.26, \"end\": 304.32, \"text\": \"It shows one-in-seven teens between the age of 12 and 17 is sexting and one-in-four has\"}, {\"start\": 304.32, \"end\": 307.8, \"text\": \"been sexted.\"}, {\"start\": 307.8, \"end\": 315.28, \"text\": \"Sexting is defined as \\\"the sending or receiving of nude or semi-nude images or sexually explicit\"}, {\"start\": 315.52, \"end\": 317.6, \"text\": \"text messages.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 317.6, \"end\": 323.8, \"text\": \"According to the study the biggest concern is the possibility of those photos or messages\"}, {\"start\": 323.8, \"end\": 327.08, \"text\": \"being spread to other people.\"}, {\"start\": 327.08, \"end\": 336.28, \"text\": \"Researchers say sexting can cause severe emotional distress and preteens can be particularly\"}, {\"start\": 336.28, \"end\": 338.56, \"text\": \"vulnerable.\"}, {\"start\": 338.56, \"end\": 343.76, \"text\": \"That's why the study suggests age-appropriate information on sexing should be part of sex\"}, {\"start\": 343.76, \"end\": 345.52, \"text\": \"education.\"}, {\"start\": 347.44, \"end\": 356.8, \"text\": \"For 15 years e-cigarettes have been billed as a safer alternative to traditional cigarettes.\"}, {\"start\": 356.8, \"end\": 368.84, \"text\": \"But a new study found e-cigs can make it harder to quit smoking.\"}, {\"start\": 368.84, \"end\": 373.64, \"text\": \"In most cases people end up vaping and smoking.\"}, {\"start\": 373.64, \"end\": 378.24, \"text\": \"The study found if you are a dual user, vaping and smoking cigarettes every day,\"}, {\"start\": 378.24, \"end\": 382.44, \"text\": \"the combined risk of a heart attack goes up five times.\"}, {\"start\": 382.44, \"end\": 384.64, \"text\": \"So if you are a smoker here's something you can do right now.\"}, {\"start\": 384.64, \"end\": 386.12, \"text\": \"Stop!\"}, {\"start\": 386.12, \"end\": 392.0, \"text\": \"Scientists say stopping smoking immediately drops your risk for a heart attack.\"}, {\"start\": 394.08, \"end\": 403.12, \"text\": \"Last October a Nebraska man named Thomas Hartman claimed he was a victim of a robbery.\"}, {\"start\": 403.12, \"end\": 409.12, \"text\": \"But detectives quickly dispelled his claim and Hartman admitted he made it up.\"}, {\"start\": 409.12, \"end\": 415.52, \"text\": \"At the same time, Hartman's girlfriend was talking to cops in the next room.\"}, {\"start\": 415.52, \"end\": 418.96, \"text\": \"Hartman started yelling to her through the wall \\\"Babe, Babe!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 418.96, \"end\": 421.68, \"text\": \"I think they're going to take me to jail!\"}, {\"start\": 421.68, \"end\": 426.72, \"text\": \"Go get that money and bond me out!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 426.72, \"end\": 435.28, \"text\": \"Then Hartman stacks a chair on the table and puts his hands in the ceiling.\"}, {\"start\": 435.28, \"end\": 438.64, \"text\": \"Police caught him in the act, thinking he was trying to escape.\"}, {\"start\": 438.64, \"end\": 443.44, \"text\": \"But it turns out authorities say he was trying to hide cocaine, which fell out of the ceiling\"}, {\"start\": 443.44, \"end\": 446.48, \"text\": \"when he was caught.\"}, {\"start\": 446.48, \"end\": 451.52, \"text\": \"Hartman's antics ended up landing him nine months probation for drug possession.\"}, {\"start\": 452.96, \"end\": 455.28, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 455.28, \"end\": 456.32, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 456.32, \"end\": 458.88, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 458.88, \"end\": 464.56, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 464.88, \"end\": 471.36, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "shFwGHIBOiA": {
    "video_id": "shFwGHIBOiA",
    "title": "Trump shifts back to hard-line immigration stance (ASL - 4.3.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180404",
    "duration": 111,
    "view_count": 120,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.18, \"end\": 13.52, \"text\": \"In the last 48 hours President Trump has tweeted 10 times about illegal immigration.\"}, {\"start\": 13.52, \"end\": 19.32, \"text\": \"He continues to complain about US immigration policies, calling current laws \\\"weak\\\" and\"}, {\"start\": 19.32, \"end\": 28.94, \"text\": \"an \\\"Obama joke\\\" and urging Congress to act.\"}, {\"start\": 28.94, \"end\": 37.78, \"text\": \"This after sources say a number of the president's allies warned him this weekend that his support\"}, {\"start\": 37.78, \"end\": 43.88, \"text\": \"base thinks he's softening on immigration.\"}, {\"start\": 43.88, \"end\": 57.84, \"text\": \"So the White House is beginning another push to pass a series of hardline measures that\"}, {\"start\": 57.84, \"end\": 66.5, \"text\": \"failed to gain steam last fall.\"}, {\"start\": 66.5, \"end\": 78.66, \"text\": \"Those measures include removing protections that prevent the immediate deportation of\"}, {\"start\": 78.66, \"end\": 86.38, \"text\": \"undocumented children and allowing authorities to keep families\"}, {\"start\": 86.38, \"end\": 108.66, \"text\": \"in detention for longer periods while they await deportation decisions.\"}]"
  },
  "0mR7n0W1h9c": {
    "video_id": "0mR7n0W1h9c",
    "title": "Texas serial bomber killed, more bombs may be in region (ASL - 3.21.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180322",
    "duration": 130,
    "view_count": 73,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.08, \"end\": 14.92, \"text\": \"Police in Texas say this man, 24-year-old Mark Anthony Conditt, is responsible for the\"}, {\"start\": 14.92, \"end\": 21.28, \"text\": \"package bombings that killed two people and injured five others this month.\"}, {\"start\": 21.28, \"end\": 29.54, \"text\": \"Police believe surveillance cameras caught Conditt dropping packages off at a FedEx facility\"}, {\"start\": 29.54, \"end\": 31.54, \"text\": \"on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 31.54, \"end\": 38.6, \"text\": \"When investigators analyzed the bombs they realize they all had something in common:\"}, {\"start\": 38.6, \"end\": 45.7, \"text\": \"they were being made from common household ingredients.\"}, {\"start\": 45.7, \"end\": 51.6, \"text\": \"So they hit the area stores and started scanning receipts.\"}, {\"start\": 51.6, \"end\": 63.16, \"text\": \"That's how they were able to track down Conditt to a hotel outside of Austin.\"}, {\"start\": 63.16, \"end\": 73.04, \"text\": \"Once Conditt realized he was surrounded, he jumped into his car and drove off.\"}, {\"start\": 73.04, \"end\": 80.98, \"text\": \"When the SWAT team started closing in on the highway, police say Conditt detonated a bomb\"}, {\"start\": 80.98, \"end\": 86.1, \"text\": \"inside his car and killed himself.\"}, {\"start\": 86.1, \"end\": 92.299, \"text\": \"Investigators searching Conditt's home say they found more homemade explosive devices.\"}, {\"start\": 92.3, \"end\": 103.12, \"text\": \"There hoping to uncover information that will shed some light on a motive for Conditt's actions.\"}, {\"start\": 103.12, \"end\": 114.2, \"text\": \"Although the suspect is dead, investigators warn the danger may still exist.\"}, {\"start\": 114.2, \"end\": 126.48, \"text\": \"Police don't know yet if Conditt had an accomplice and there is a possibility more bombs may\"}, {\"start\": 126.48, \"end\": 129.22, \"text\": \"still be in the area.\"}]"
  },
  "09_WhZGpLrE": {
    "video_id": "09_WhZGpLrE",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.17.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180217",
    "duration": 489,
    "view_count": 1421,
    "description": "2.17.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-New details about Florida shooter’s dark past\n-Trump visits Florida shooting victims, first responders\n-Mueller indicts 13 Russians for US election meddling\n-Lindsey Vonn responds to internet trolls\n-Harry Connick Jr’s talk show canceled\n-Spectacular sunrise above the fog!\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and inf",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.66, \"end\": 7.84, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.84, \"end\": 9.68, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 9.76, \"end\": 11.26, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.26, \"end\": 14.36, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.72, \"end\": 31.66, \"text\": \"Investigators are getting new insight into the dark mind of Florida school shooter Nikolas Cruz.\"}, {\"start\": 31.76, \"end\": 45.38, \"text\": \"Group chat messages show he was obsessed with race, violence, and guns.\"}, {\"start\": 45.38, \"end\": 53.02, \"text\": \"At one point he said \\\"I hate Jews, N-words, immigrants.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 53.02, \"end\": 60.82, \"text\": \"He also talked about killing Mexicans, keeping black people in chains and cutting their necks.\"}, {\"start\": 60.82, \"end\": 68.9, \"text\": \"Police documents show his mother had repeatedly called police to the home.\"}, {\"start\": 68.9, \"end\": 75.02, \"text\": \"One incident report describes Cruz as suffering from mental illness and being \\\"emotionally\"}, {\"start\": 75.02, \"end\": 77.64, \"text\": \"handicapped.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 77.7, \"end\": 84.94, \"text\": \"And none of this was enough to stop him from passing a background check and buying an AR-15\"}, {\"start\": 84.94, \"end\": 88.24, \"text\": \"semi-automatic rifle.\"}, {\"start\": 88.24, \"end\": 96.38, \"text\": \"We also learned today that the public defender assigned to Cruz's case plans to enter a guilty\"}, {\"start\": 96.38, \"end\": 110.58, \"text\": \"plea in order to avoid the death penalty and a long, painful trial for the community.\"}, {\"start\": 113.62, \"end\": 121.84, \"text\": \"Yesterday President Trump and first lady Melania Trump arrived in Florida to meet with victims\"}, {\"start\": 121.84, \"end\": 125.58, \"text\": \"and first responders in the Florida mass shooting.\"}, {\"start\": 125.6, \"end\": 132.46, \"text\": \"They met with medical staff at a hospital where many of the victims were treated.\"}, {\"start\": 132.46, \"end\": 146.14, \"text\": \"They also met with first responders and emergency personnel, thanking them for their heroism Wednesday.\"}, {\"start\": 146.14, \"end\": 152.0, \"text\": \"The president's visit comes on the same day that the first three of the 17 victims are\"}, {\"start\": 152.0, \"end\": 153.66, \"text\": \"laid to rest.\"}, {\"start\": 153.66, \"end\": 160.28, \"text\": \"But for the past two days, many people in the Parkland community have said time and\"}, {\"start\": 160.28, \"end\": 164.56, \"text\": \"time again it's not just thoughts and prayers they want.\"}, {\"start\": 164.56, \"end\": 168.3, \"text\": \"They want action from the government.\"}, {\"start\": 168.3, \"end\": 175.68, \"text\": \"They are demanding changes that will keep children and the community safe.\"}, {\"start\": 179.56, \"end\": 190.42, \"text\": \"A grand jury has indicted 13 Russian nationals and three Russian groups for alleged meddling\"}, {\"start\": 190.42, \"end\": 193.82, \"text\": \"in the 2016 US presidential election.\"}, {\"start\": 193.82, \"end\": 202.9, \"text\": \"The indictment alleges the Russians posed as American citizens, operated social media\"}, {\"start\": 202.9, \"end\": 210.25, \"text\": \"accounts aimed at US audiences and set up rallies around the US.\"}, {\"start\": 210.25, \"end\": 216.379, \"text\": \"They allegedly manipulated information about a number of candidates, but by mid-2016 supported\"}, {\"start\": 216.38, \"end\": 221.28, \"text\": \"Trump and disparaged Hillary Clinton.\"}, {\"start\": 221.28, \"end\": 228.04, \"text\": \"The charges are the result of Special Counsel Robert Mueller's investigation looking into\"}, {\"start\": 228.04, \"end\": 233.76, \"text\": \"Russian meddling in the 2016 campaign, including any connections between Russia and the Trump\"}, {\"start\": 233.76, \"end\": 235.02, \"text\": \"campaign.\"}, {\"start\": 235.02, \"end\": 245.08, \"text\": \"The president has long dismissed talk of Russian interference in the election as a hoax.\"}, {\"start\": 245.08, \"end\": 254.66, \"text\": \"A Russian Foreign Ministry spokeswoman has called the indictments absurd.\"}, {\"start\": 257.4, \"end\": 268.18, \"text\": \"Olympic skier Lindsey Vonn had a very disappointing day during her first event of the winter Olympics.\"}, {\"start\": 268.18, \"end\": 277.52, \"text\": \"She made a costly mistake on the last turn of the women's Super-G competition and she\"}, {\"start\": 277.52, \"end\": 281.64, \"text\": \"ended up out of medal contention in sixth place.\"}, {\"start\": 281.64, \"end\": 287.3, \"text\": \"That's when the online abuse started -- again.\"}, {\"start\": 287.3, \"end\": 293.6, \"text\": \"If you remember back in December, Vonn said if she won a medal at the winter Olympics,\"}, {\"start\": 293.6, \"end\": 296.46, \"text\": \"she would not visit the White House.\"}, {\"start\": 296.46, \"end\": 305.14, \"text\": \"Negative comments poured in on Twitter, with one user saying he hoped Vonn would break\"}, {\"start\": 305.14, \"end\": 307.3, \"text\": \"her neck during the Olympics.\"}, {\"start\": 307.3, \"end\": 317.28, \"text\": \"Today Vonn responded to her twitter trolls by posting this: \\\"Frustrating to be so close\"}, {\"start\": 317.28, \"end\": 324.72, \"text\": \"to the podium and to have made such a big mistake, but that's ski racing.\"}, {\"start\": 324.72, \"end\": 331.06, \"text\": \"I'm proud of the way I skied and how I attacked course.\"}, {\"start\": 331.06, \"end\": 335.68, \"text\": \"I gave it my all and came up short.\"}, {\"start\": 335.68, \"end\": 337.26, \"text\": \"That's life.\"}, {\"start\": 337.26, \"end\": 341.02, \"text\": \"Now it's on to the downhill.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 343.66, \"end\": 352.68, \"text\": \"Harry Connick Jr's daytime talk show is ending its two-year run.\"}, {\"start\": 352.68, \"end\": 359.84, \"text\": \"Executives with NBC Universal say the show will go off the air in September.\"}, {\"start\": 359.84, \"end\": 367.0, \"text\": \"The show premiered in September 2016 but failed to click ratings-wise with viewers.\"}, {\"start\": 367.0, \"end\": 374.14, \"text\": \"Connick said that he is incredibly proud of the show and that he will look for new avenues\"}, {\"start\": 374.14, \"end\": 385.08, \"text\": \"to help the nation, including a starring role in the stage musical version of the classic\"}, {\"start\": 385.08, \"end\": 387.96, \"text\": \"film \\\"The Sting.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 391.08, \"end\": 402.76, \"text\": \"Cameras at Haleakala National Park in Hawaii captured a spectacular sunrise on Sunday!\"}, {\"start\": 402.76, \"end\": 409.68, \"text\": \"You can see thick, white fog rolling below while the sky above is splashed with brilliant\"}, {\"start\": 409.68, \"end\": 417.88, \"text\": \"colors -- blue, gold, orange, red, gray.\"}, {\"start\": 417.88, \"end\": 422.22, \"text\": \"And then all of a sudden, the sun makes its grand entrance above.\"}, {\"start\": 422.22, \"end\": 425.1, \"text\": \"It's only 30 seconds of time-lapsed video.\"}, {\"start\": 425.2, \"end\": 435.12, \"text\": \"But its worth pausing the hustle and bustle of your day to just sit, watch and enjoy.\"}, {\"start\": 464.06, \"end\": 466.42, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 466.42, \"end\": 467.9, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 467.9, \"end\": 469.9, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 469.9, \"end\": 474.34, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 474.34, \"end\": 481.26, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "KW7GMZvZSdY": {
    "video_id": "KW7GMZvZSdY",
    "title": "Dining out may disrupt your hormones (ASL - 4.3.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180404",
    "duration": 127,
    "view_count": 587,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.14, \"end\": 8.54, \"text\": \"We all know home-cooked meals are probably healthier than restaurant food.\"}, {\"start\": 8.54, \"end\": 17.64, \"text\": \"But according to a new study published in the Journal Environment International, dining\"}, {\"start\": 17.64, \"end\": 25.73, \"text\": \"out increases your exposure to potentially harmful chemicals.\"}, {\"start\": 25.73, \"end\": 37.74, \"text\": \"Those chemicals are called phthalates and researchers say they can make your hormones\"}, {\"start\": 37.74, \"end\": 40.98, \"text\": \"go haywire.\"}, {\"start\": 40.98, \"end\": 58.24, \"text\": \"The study found people who ate at restaurants and fast food outlets often had 35% higher\"}, {\"start\": 58.24, \"end\": 61.3, \"text\": \"levels of phthalates than those who didn't.\"}, {\"start\": 61.3, \"end\": 67.5, \"text\": \"Research shows that eating foods with high levels of those chemicals have been linked\"}, {\"start\": 67.5, \"end\": 70.26, \"text\": \"to birth defects.\"}, {\"start\": 70.26, \"end\": 80.68, \"text\": \"And now scientists suspect the chemicals can disrupt hormones and cause fertility problems.\"}, {\"start\": 80.68, \"end\": 85.62, \"text\": \"Researchers say the food is likely contaminated with those chemicals because it comes in contact\"}, {\"start\": 85.62, \"end\": 92.52, \"text\": \"with gloves and plastic packaging.\"}, {\"start\": 92.54, \"end\": 102.5, \"text\": \"Those same synthetic chemicals are also found in perfumes, hair sprays and shampoos.\"}, {\"start\": 102.5, \"end\": 106.26, \"text\": \"But there is good news!\"}, {\"start\": 106.26, \"end\": 112.56, \"text\": \"Those chemicals only stay in the body for about a day.\"}, {\"start\": 112.56, \"end\": 116.62, \"text\": \"So don't eliminate eating out altogether.\"}, {\"start\": 116.76, \"end\": 125.58, \"text\": \"Just try to mix in good home-cooked meals every now and again.\"}]"
  },
  "YfZAuGEaDWg": {
    "video_id": "YfZAuGEaDWg",
    "title": "Repair your credit, beware of scammers (ASL - 3.22.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180323",
    "duration": 117,
    "view_count": 184,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.94, \"end\": 3.98, \"text\": \"What's your credit score?\"}, {\"start\": 4.0, \"end\": 8.68, \"text\": \"If you want to make your score better, be careful.\"}, {\"start\": 8.68, \"end\": 18.84, \"text\": \"Scammers can not only steal your information but may also turn you into a crook.\"}, {\"start\": 18.84, \"end\": 26.92, \"text\": \"According to the Federal Trade Commission there are a few easy ways to spot a credit\"}, {\"start\": 26.98, \"end\": 30.74, \"text\": \"repair scam.\"}, {\"start\": 30.82, \"end\": 38.7, \"text\": \"First -- if the company asked for payment before they render any services.\"}, {\"start\": 38.7, \"end\": 46.0, \"text\": \"Also if they ask that you do not contact the credit reporting agencies directly.\"}, {\"start\": 46.0, \"end\": 55.56, \"text\": \"And if they suggest giving false information when applying for a mortgage or loan.\"}, {\"start\": 55.56, \"end\": 64.54, \"text\": \"Another troubling trend among credit repair scammers is the promise of an entirely new\"}, {\"start\": 64.54, \"end\": 69.64, \"text\": \"credit identity, which can unwittingly land a consumer in trouble with the law.\"}, {\"start\": 69.64, \"end\": 77.9, \"text\": \"You can spot these scams when a service suggests you don't use your Social Security number\"}, {\"start\": 77.9, \"end\": 80.68, \"text\": \"as a primary source of identification.\"}, {\"start\": 80.68, \"end\": 89.0, \"text\": \"Instead they want you to use a new number they assign called a \\\"credit privacy number\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 89.0, \"end\": 93.08, \"text\": \"or \\\"credit profile number\\\" (CPN).\"}, {\"start\": 93.08, \"end\": 98.72, \"text\": \"In many cases these numbers are stolen Social Security numbers, often from children, which\"}, {\"start\": 98.72, \"end\": 103.2, \"text\": \"is why they have a clean credit slate.\"}, {\"start\": 103.2, \"end\": 112.66, \"text\": \"And it can turn an innocent consumer into an unknowing identity thief.\"}, {\"start\": 112.74, \"end\": 115.42, \"text\": \"So be careful.\"}]"
  },
  "0PSmYAx9Dr0": {
    "video_id": "0PSmYAx9Dr0",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.5.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180106",
    "duration": 566,
    "view_count": 1253,
    "description": "1.5.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nToday's Headlines:\n-\"Fire and Fury\" sells out quickly (1.5.18)\n-White House asks to screen movie \"The Post\" (1.5.18)\n-Brutal cold follows \"Bomb Cyclone\" (1.5.18)\n-Stay warm, your life depends on it (1.5.18)\n-Olympian arrested for lewd acts on child (1.5.18)\n-Feds investigating Clinton Foundation (1.5.18)\n-2018 tax filings accepted on January 29th (1.5.18)\n-Obama to be 1st guest on Letterman's new show (1.5.18)",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.98, \"end\": 8.88, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.88, \"end\": 10.48, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.5, \"end\": 11.36, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 11.36, \"end\": 13.52, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 16.06, \"end\": 26.9, \"text\": \"The highly-controversial book \\\"Fire and Fury\\\" hit store shelves today.\"}, {\"start\": 26.9, \"end\": 29.14, \"text\": \"But good luck getting your hands on a copy.\"}, {\"start\": 29.14, \"end\": 36.74, \"text\": \"Bookstores and online retailers say the book sold out quickly and it could take 2 to 4\"}, {\"start\": 36.78, \"end\": 39.52, \"text\": \"weeks to restock.\"}, {\"start\": 39.52, \"end\": 55.32, \"text\": \"The tell-all book claims there is chaos inside the White House, it claims Trump is mentally\"}, {\"start\": 55.32, \"end\": 60.1, \"text\": \"unfit to run the country and claims Trump's marriage to First Lady Melania Trump is dysfunctional.\"}, {\"start\": 60.1, \"end\": 67.54, \"text\": \"The book also contains stunning allegations about the president's first-hand involvement\"}, {\"start\": 67.54, \"end\": 72.3, \"text\": \"in crafting a misleading statement about the now-infamous June 2016 meeting between top\"}, {\"start\": 72.3, \"end\": 74.74, \"text\": \"Trump staffers and Russians.\"}, {\"start\": 74.74, \"end\": 79.56, \"text\": \"The Trump administration says the book is phony and full of lies and it is attempting\"}, {\"start\": 79.56, \"end\": 82.68, \"text\": \"to discredit the book.\"}, {\"start\": 85.82, \"end\": 91.42, \"text\": \"The new movie \\\"The Post\\\" is coming to the White House.\"}, {\"start\": 91.42, \"end\": 99.0, \"text\": \"The \\\"Hollywood Reporter\\\" says President Trump's team has been granted access to the movie\"}, {\"start\": 99.0, \"end\": 103.02, \"text\": \"for both the White House and Camp David.\"}, {\"start\": 103.02, \"end\": 110.32, \"text\": \"It's unclear if Trump himself will view the film, but Hollywood studios traditionally\"}, {\"start\": 110.32, \"end\": 118.04, \"text\": \"provide movies for the first family or White House staff to watch when asked.\"}, {\"start\": 118.04, \"end\": 126.7, \"text\": \"\\\"The Post\\\" looks back at the 1971 decision by the \\\"Washington Post\\\" to publish the top-secret\"}, {\"start\": 126.7, \"end\": 130.63, \"text\": \"Pentagon papers.\"}, {\"start\": 130.63, \"end\": 141.54, \"text\": \"The movie stars Meryl Streep and Tom Hanks, who have both been outspoken on their opposition\"}, {\"start\": 141.54, \"end\": 143.48, \"text\": \"to Trump.\"}, {\"start\": 143.48, \"end\": 148.84, \"text\": \"Hanks himself has said he would not accept an invitation to watch the film at the White\"}, {\"start\": 148.84, \"end\": 151.32, \"text\": \"House is Trump is in office.\"}, {\"start\": 154.16, \"end\": 160.0, \"text\": \"First came the snow and freezing rain.\"}, {\"start\": 160.0, \"end\": 164.04, \"text\": \"Now comes the dangerous cold.\"}, {\"start\": 164.12, \"end\": 172.8, \"text\": \"Millions of people along the East Coast will see temperatures plummet to single digits.\"}, {\"start\": 172.8, \"end\": 178.44, \"text\": \"And the windchill will make it feel even colder.\"}, {\"start\": 178.44, \"end\": 185.28, \"text\": \"Places like Boston, Hampton Beach and others are flooding with freezing water from the\"}, {\"start\": 185.32, \"end\": 189.04, \"text\": \"Atlantic.\"}, {\"start\": 189.04, \"end\": 191.96, \"text\": \"To make matters worse once the water gets on land, the cold air and snow turns into\"}, {\"start\": 191.96, \"end\": 194.6, \"text\": \"an icy mass.\"}, {\"start\": 194.6, \"end\": 197.72, \"text\": \"And it is not just roads.\"}, {\"start\": 197.76, \"end\": 204.2, \"text\": \"More than 4,000 flights to and from the region have been canceled.\"}, {\"start\": 204.2, \"end\": 216.2, \"text\": \"LaGuardia and JFK airports are close entirely because of heavy snow.\"}, {\"start\": 216.2, \"end\": 224.64, \"text\": \"As the arctic air blankets the region, many plan to stay indoors just to stay safe.\"}, {\"start\": 227.72, \"end\": 235.88, \"text\": \"Staying warm during the winter months is vital to your health and your life.\"}, {\"start\": 235.96, \"end\": 241.36, \"text\": \"When the body is warm it doesn't have to work as hard to keep important organs like the\"}, {\"start\": 241.36, \"end\": 245.76, \"text\": \"heart, brain and lungs warm.\"}, {\"start\": 245.84, \"end\": 251.6, \"text\": \"But when it's cold, blood vessels in all different parts of the body constrict to try to preserve\"}, {\"start\": 251.6, \"end\": 253.44, \"text\": \"heat.\"}, {\"start\": 253.44, \"end\": 259.48, \"text\": \"And when the body's blood vessels narrow, the risk of a heart attack increases.\"}, {\"start\": 259.48, \"end\": 271.96, \"text\": \"Wintry weather has also been associated with asthma symptoms, frostbite and hypothermia.\"}, {\"start\": 271.96, \"end\": 280.48, \"text\": \"Shoveling snow is one example of high risk activity that can be deadly during cold weather.\"}, {\"start\": 280.48, \"end\": 285.16, \"text\": \"Don't overdo it.\"}, {\"start\": 285.16, \"end\": 289.12, \"text\": \"Take breaks and get help.\"}, {\"start\": 289.12, \"end\": 298.04, \"text\": \"Also check on elderly neighbors to make sure they have proper heating.\"}, {\"start\": 298.04, \"end\": 303.04, \"text\": \"Knocking on their door can literally save a life.\"}, {\"start\": 306.16, \"end\": 326.72, \"text\": \"Authorities in California have charged 1984 Olympic gold medalist boxer Paul Garza Gonzales\"}, {\"start\": 326.72, \"end\": 329.28, \"text\": \"with child sex abuse.\"}, {\"start\": 329.28, \"end\": 335.4, \"text\": \"The 53-year-old was arrested last week and charged with eight felony counts, including\"}, {\"start\": 335.4, \"end\": 343.52, \"text\": \"four counts of lewd acts on a child.\"}, {\"start\": 343.52, \"end\": 350.16, \"text\": \"For the past 10 years Gonzales has worked as a boxing coach for the Los Angeles County\"}, {\"start\": 350.16, \"end\": 353.16, \"text\": \"Parks and Recreation department.\"}, {\"start\": 353.16, \"end\": 358.76, \"text\": \"Police believe there may be other victims.\"}, {\"start\": 358.76, \"end\": 366.0, \"text\": \"Gonzales is behind bars and has a court appearance scheduled for January 18th.\"}, {\"start\": 369.6, \"end\": 379.4, \"text\": \"Federal authorities are investigating the Clinton Foundation.\"}, {\"start\": 379.4, \"end\": 390.52, \"text\": \"FBI and federal prosecutors are investigating whether Foundation donors were improperly\"}, {\"start\": 390.52, \"end\": 396.16, \"text\": \"promised favors or access to Hillary Clinton when she was Secretary of State.\"}, {\"start\": 396.16, \"end\": 401.56, \"text\": \"In addition, the investigation is looking into whether any of the Foundation's tax exempt\"}, {\"start\": 401.56, \"end\": 405.24, \"text\": \"funds were misused.\"}, {\"start\": 405.24, \"end\": 408.72, \"text\": \"It's not clear what sparked the new investigation.\"}, {\"start\": 408.88, \"end\": 414.84, \"text\": \"The previous investigation stalled prior to last year's presidential election.\"}, {\"start\": 414.84, \"end\": 421.16, \"text\": \"A Clinton Foundation spokesperson says the investigation is politically motivated and\"}, {\"start\": 421.28, \"end\": 423.72, \"text\": \"unfounded.\"}, {\"start\": 426.28, \"end\": 434.04, \"text\": \"The IRS says it will soon start accepting income tax returns.\"}, {\"start\": 434.04, \"end\": 441.36, \"text\": \"The agency says 2017 federal income tax returns can be filed as early as January 29th.\"}, {\"start\": 441.36, \"end\": 452.08, \"text\": \"Normally April 15th is the final filing deadline but it falls on Sunday this year.\"}, {\"start\": 452.12, \"end\": 463.92, \"text\": \"And Monday, April 16th, is Emancipation Day, a legal holiday in Washington DC.\"}, {\"start\": 463.92, \"end\": 470.38, \"text\": \"So the deadline to file is April 17th this year.\"}, {\"start\": 470.38, \"end\": 477.4, \"text\": \"The IRS believes it will issue the vast majority of refunds within 21 days of a return being\"}, {\"start\": 477.4, \"end\": 479.72, \"text\": \"filed.\"}, {\"start\": 481.72, \"end\": 492.16, \"text\": \"Former President Barack Obama will be the first guest on David Letterman's new Netflix\"}, {\"start\": 492.16, \"end\": 493.24, \"text\": \"talkshow.\"}, {\"start\": 493.36, \"end\": 500.64, \"text\": \"It would be Obama's first television talkshow appearance since leaving office.\"}, {\"start\": 500.64, \"end\": 516.76, \"text\": \"The show, entitled \\\"My Next Guest Needs No Introduction\\\", launches January 12th.\"}, {\"start\": 516.76, \"end\": 530.32, \"text\": \"It's an hour-long, six-episode series with a new show each month.\"}, {\"start\": 530.32, \"end\": 542.72, \"text\": \"Other high profile guest include Tina Fey, Jay-Z and George Clooney.\"}, {\"start\": 545.04, \"end\": 546.92, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 546.92, \"end\": 548.04, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 548.04, \"end\": 549.8, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 549.8, \"end\": 553.28, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 553.28, \"end\": 558.68, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-bvpPL0vdz0": {
    "video_id": "-bvpPL0vdz0",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.28.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20181029",
    "duration": 478,
    "view_count": 1215,
    "description": "Sponsor: Georgia Vocational Rehabilitation Agency - https://gvs.georgia.gov/\n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-11 killed in mass shooting at synagogue\n-Pittsburgh teams react to synagogue shooting\n-Leicester City soccer team owner's chopper crashes \n-Migrants demand entry at Mexico border\n-Weekend box office\n-Today is National Chocolate Day\n\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provid",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.209, \"end\": 7.599, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.599, \"end\": 10.42, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.42, \"end\": 11.86, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 11.86, \"end\": 16.92, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for the day.\"}, {\"start\": 18.62, \"end\": 27.48, \"text\": \"Police say 46-year-old Robert Bowers walked into the Tree of Life synagogue and opened\"}, {\"start\": 27.48, \"end\": 31.079, \"text\": \"fire yesterday morning.\"}, {\"start\": 31.08, \"end\": 37.08, \"text\": \"11 people are dead and six were injured, including\"}, {\"start\": 37.08, \"end\": 38.76, \"text\": \"four police officers who responded to the scene.\"}, {\"start\": 38.76, \"end\": 42.98, \"text\": \"Bowers was taken into custody and is now hospitalized with gunshot wounds.\"}, {\"start\": 42.98, \"end\": 51.14, \"text\": \"According to police, Bowers made anti-semitic statements during the shooting and targeted\"}, {\"start\": 51.14, \"end\": 53.26, \"text\": \"Jews in posts on social media.\"}, {\"start\": 53.26, \"end\": 70.14, \"text\": \"Bowers faces 29 charges, including 11 counts of using a firearm to commit murder and hate\"}, {\"start\": 70.15, \"end\": 73.399, \"text\": \"crimes charges.\"}, {\"start\": 73.399, \"end\": 78.92, \"text\": \"He could face the death penalty if he is convicted of a hate crime.\"}, {\"start\": 78.92, \"end\": 83.93, \"text\": \"President Trump, who is expected to visit Pittsburgh, condemned the deadly shooting\"}, {\"start\": 83.93, \"end\": 98.54, \"text\": \"during a rally in Indianapolis.\"}, {\"start\": 98.54, \"end\": 110.7, \"text\": \"Pittsburgh's Pro sports community is responding on Twitter reacting to yesterday's mass shooting\"}, {\"start\": 110.72, \"end\": 114.46, \"text\": \"at the Tree of Life synagogue.\"}, {\"start\": 114.46, \"end\": 123.26, \"text\": \"Pro hockey's, Pittsburgh Penguins wrote that they were incredibly saddened to hear of the\"}, {\"start\": 123.26, \"end\": 125.6, \"text\": \"tragedy.\"}, {\"start\": 125.6, \"end\": 145.38, \"text\": \"Baseball's Pittsburgh Pirates said their hearts broke at the news.\"}, {\"start\": 145.38, \"end\": 164.64, \"text\": \"The Jewish Star of David replaces the top yellow diamond on the logo that is synonymous\"}, {\"start\": 164.64, \"end\": 169.42, \"text\": \"with the Pittsburgh Steelers.\"}, {\"start\": 169.42, \"end\": 178.64, \"text\": \"The image has been shared on Twitter, as users express messages of support with the hashtag\"}, {\"start\": 178.64, \"end\": 187.48, \"text\": \"#stronger than hate.\"}, {\"start\": 190.66, \"end\": 200.44, \"text\": \"It is still unknown whether, or not Leicester City's soccer team owner, Thai billionaire,\"}, {\"start\": 200.44, \"end\": 209.68, \"text\": \"Vichai Srivaddhanaprabha is alive.\"}, {\"start\": 209.68, \"end\": 227.72, \"text\": \"Yesterday, his helicopter crashed in a parking lot next to the stadium, and burst into flames.\"}, {\"start\": 227.72, \"end\": 239.04, \"text\": \"Witnesses say the helicopter had barely cleared the stadium walls before making a loud noise\"}, {\"start\": 239.04, \"end\": 241.24, \"text\": \"and crashing.\"}, {\"start\": 241.24, \"end\": 248.34, \"text\": \"Vachai regularly took off from the center circle on his way back to his home in London\"}, {\"start\": 248.34, \"end\": 249.76, \"text\": \"after home games.\"}, {\"start\": 249.76, \"end\": 261.76, \"text\": \"The police have not revealed whether the 60-year-old billionaire was on board the flight.\"}, {\"start\": 261.76, \"end\": 269.84, \"text\": \"A second migrant caravan is waiting to be allowed into Mexico.\"}, {\"start\": 269.84, \"end\": 279.35, \"text\": \"More than 2,000 migrants from Central America arrived at the Guatemalan-Mexican border.\"}, {\"start\": 279.35, \"end\": 286.759, \"text\": \"Authorities from both countries deployed riot police to prevent them from crossing into\"}, {\"start\": 286.759, \"end\": 293.509, \"text\": \"Mexico on the way to the United States.\"}, {\"start\": 293.509, \"end\": 302.04, \"text\": \"Despite their plea to be allowed in, the gates remain close.\"}, {\"start\": 302.04, \"end\": 313.2, \"text\": \"Migrants in the caravan have said they are fleeing poverty and violence.\"}, {\"start\": 313.2, \"end\": 333.77, \"text\": \"And they are not deterred by the Trump administration's plans to do to deploy troops to the border.\"}, {\"start\": 333.77, \"end\": 339.65, \"text\": \"These are the top three box office movies this week.\"}, {\"start\": 339.65, \"end\": 348.6, \"text\": \"The horror sequel, Halloween is number one on the list.\"}, {\"start\": 348.6, \"end\": 355.719, \"text\": \"It made $127 million in 10 days.\"}, {\"start\": 355.719, \"end\": 371.879, \"text\": \"In second place is A Star is Born for the fourth straight weekend earning $14.1 million.\"}, {\"start\": 371.879, \"end\": 386.789, \"text\": \"Third-place is Venom, earning $187 million worldwide.\"}, {\"start\": 386.789, \"end\": 392.319, \"text\": \"Today is national chocolate day.\"}, {\"start\": 392.32, \"end\": 400.96, \"text\": \"While there are many chocolate related holidays throughout the year this is the one day to\"}, {\"start\": 400.96, \"end\": 406.68, \"text\": \"celebrate everything chocolate.\"}, {\"start\": 406.68, \"end\": 411.99, \"text\": \"Chocolate comes from the seed of a cocoa tree.\"}, {\"start\": 411.99, \"end\": 424.199, \"text\": \"The earliest known documentation of humans using the cocoa seeds date back to 1100 BC.\"}, {\"start\": 424.199, \"end\": 430.819, \"text\": \"Since then we've perfected the art of cooking with chocolate.\"}, {\"start\": 430.82, \"end\": 447.12, \"text\": \"So, whether you prefer your chocolate baked brownies, cakes or cookies go ahead and indulge.\"}, {\"start\": 450.1, \"end\": 452.78, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 452.78, \"end\": 454.88, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 455.0, \"end\": 456.92, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 456.92, \"end\": 460.9, \"text\": \"And remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 461.0, \"end\": 464.2, \"text\": \"Sign1news.\"}, {\"start\": 464.2, \"end\": 465.78, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 465.78, \"end\": 468.64, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-GgW0Hrt6ow": {
    "video_id": "-GgW0Hrt6ow",
    "title": "Sign1News 6.24.19 - News for the Deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20190625",
    "duration": 449,
    "view_count": 1321,
    "description": "TODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-10th American dies in Dominican Republic\n-2,000 people win lottery by picking 0-0-0-0\n-Charlottesville attacker asks for mercy\n-Cat survives 35-minute tumble in washing machine\n-NBA honors Magic Johnson and Larry Bird",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 29.28, \"end\": 30.42, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 30.42, \"end\": 31.96, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 31.96, \"end\": 33.74, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 33.74, \"end\": 35.84, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 39.36, \"end\": 47.5, \"text\": \"For the 10th time in the past 13 months, an American death is linked to the Dominican Republic.\"}, {\"start\": 47.52, \"end\": 59.98, \"text\": \"Vittorio Caruso of New York died last week according to CNN affiliate News 12 Long Island.\"}, {\"start\": 60.0, \"end\": 65.86, \"text\": \"Family members told the station that Caruso died after falling victim to respiratory distress.\"}, {\"start\": 65.86, \"end\": 69.3, \"text\": \"He may have also had a heart attack.\"}, {\"start\": 69.3, \"end\": 78.3, \"text\": \"Dominican Republic officials said that the 10 traveler deaths are isolated events.\"}, {\"start\": 78.32, \"end\": 85.94, \"text\": \"Two of the victims were reportedly found at the Hard Rock Hotel and Casino in Punta Cana.\"}, {\"start\": 85.94, \"end\": 96.16, \"text\": \"On Sunday, the resort said it would remove alcoholic dispensers located in guestroom minibars.\"}, {\"start\": 96.16, \"end\": 104.88, \"text\": \"The resort says the decision was made independently and not as a result of the incidents.\"}, {\"start\": 111.08, \"end\": 115.72, \"text\": \"Everyone knows about lucky seven.\"}, {\"start\": 115.72, \"end\": 120.64, \"text\": \"How about lucky zero?\"}, {\"start\": 120.64, \"end\": 134.54, \"text\": \"There were more than 2,000 winning tickets Saturday for the North Carolina Pick 4 lottery's\"}, {\"start\": 134.54, \"end\": 135.86, \"text\": \"$7.8 million jackpot.\"}, {\"start\": 135.86, \"end\": 140.84, \"text\": \"And the winning numbers were 0,0,0,0.\"}, {\"start\": 140.84, \"end\": 146.4, \"text\": \"All 2,014 winners will get a share of the jackpot.\"}, {\"start\": 146.4, \"end\": 151.36, \"text\": \"The North Carolina education lottery said in a press release that it's the largest ever\"}, {\"start\": 151.36, \"end\": 156.88, \"text\": \"amount in a single drawing.\"}, {\"start\": 161.2, \"end\": 167.4, \"text\": \"22-year old James Fields Jr, the man who drove into a crowd of counter-protesters at the\"}, {\"start\": 167.4, \"end\": 174.16, \"text\": \"\\\"Unite The Right\\\" rally in Charlottesville, Virginia, is asking for mercy.\"}, {\"start\": 174.16, \"end\": 182.24, \"text\": \"In August 2017, Fields took part in the demonstrations by white nationalist and neo-Nazis.\"}, {\"start\": 182.24, \"end\": 188.4, \"text\": \"During the day of violent clashes, Fields drove his car into a crowd of people, injuring\"}, {\"start\": 188.4, \"end\": 190.28, \"text\": \"dozens and killing a woman.\"}, {\"start\": 190.28, \"end\": 198.56, \"text\": \"He was convicted on state charges of first-degree murder and other charges.\"}, {\"start\": 198.56, \"end\": 203.2, \"text\": \"Sentencing in that case is set for mid-July.\"}, {\"start\": 203.2, \"end\": 209.06, \"text\": \"On the federal level, Fields pleaded guilty to 29 hate crimes in a plea deal to avoid\"}, {\"start\": 209.06, \"end\": 212.78, \"text\": \"the death penalty.\"}, {\"start\": 212.78, \"end\": 219.04, \"text\": \"The federal sentencing is set for this Friday, June 28.\"}, {\"start\": 219.04, \"end\": 228.26, \"text\": \"Last Friday Fields filed a sentencing memo for his federal hate crimes case asking for\"}, {\"start\": 228.26, \"end\": 237.44, \"text\": \"less than life in prison because of his young age, history of mental illness and childhood trauma.\"}, {\"start\": 242.48, \"end\": 252.56, \"text\": \"This cat named Felix got stuck in a washing machine for a full 35 minute cycle and lived\"}, {\"start\": 252.56, \"end\": 253.84, \"text\": \"to tell the tale.\"}, {\"start\": 253.84, \"end\": 263.48, \"text\": \"Felix's owner says she always makes sure none of her three cats are in the washer and dryer\"}, {\"start\": 263.48, \"end\": 266.14, \"text\": \"when she's doing laundry.\"}, {\"start\": 266.14, \"end\": 274.08, \"text\": \"But last week she forgot and Felix somehow found his way inside the washer.\"}, {\"start\": 274.08, \"end\": 279.86, \"text\": \"After finding him, the family rushed him to an emergency vet.\"}, {\"start\": 279.86, \"end\": 288.34, \"text\": \"He temporarily lost his vision and had pneumonia from all the water in his lungs.\"}, {\"start\": 288.34, \"end\": 290.52, \"text\": \"But he's doing much better now.\"}, {\"start\": 290.52, \"end\": 296.06, \"text\": \"He can see again and has started eating but he remains on oxygen.\"}, {\"start\": 296.06, \"end\": 300.52, \"text\": \"The vets are expecting a full recovery.\"}, {\"start\": 300.52, \"end\": 306.42, \"text\": \"Even so, Felix's owner says she will never forgive herself and this is going to haunt\"}, {\"start\": 306.42, \"end\": 308.48, \"text\": \"her for the rest of her life.\"}, {\"start\": 308.48, \"end\": 316.6, \"text\": \"Her daughter started a Go-Fund-Me to offset the medical costs.\"}, {\"start\": 316.6, \"end\": 325.68, \"text\": \"So far it's raised nearly $9,000 towards a $10,000 goal.\"}, {\"start\": 332.12, \"end\": 338.96, \"text\": \"The National Basketball Association honors two of its biggest legends today (Monday).\"}, {\"start\": 338.96, \"end\": 353.24, \"text\": \"Earvin \\\"Magic\\\" Johnson and Larry Bird will share this year's NBA Lifetime Achievement award.\"}, {\"start\": 353.24, \"end\": 359.4, \"text\": \"This marks the first time the league has bestowed this award to two players at the same time.\"}, {\"start\": 359.4, \"end\": 364.32, \"text\": \"Both former players are already in the Hall of Fame.\"}, {\"start\": 364.32, \"end\": 372.82, \"text\": \"Johnson and Bird and their teams, the Los Angeles Lakers and Boston Celtics, respectively,\"}, {\"start\": 372.82, \"end\": 377.12, \"text\": \"duked it out throughout the 1980s.\"}, {\"start\": 377.12, \"end\": 390.04, \"text\": \"Some analysts say their rivalry helped bring basketball to the masses, making it must-see TV.\"}, {\"start\": 390.04, \"end\": 395.9, \"text\": \"Prior to playing in the pros, Johnson and Bird faced off in college.\"}, {\"start\": 395.9, \"end\": 407.66, \"text\": \"Johnson's Michigan State Spartans beat Bird's Indiana State Sycamores in the 1979\"}, {\"start\": 407.66, \"end\": 410.56, \"text\": \"NCAA championship.\"}, {\"start\": 410.56, \"end\": 418.34, \"text\": \"Bird later said that game was \\\"the toughest loss I ever took.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 421.3, \"end\": 423.32, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 423.32, \"end\": 424.58, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 424.58, \"end\": 426.36, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 426.36, \"end\": 432.86, \"text\": \"Remember to follow us on all of our social media platforms and be sure to download our\"}, {\"start\": 432.86, \"end\": 434.52, \"text\": \"apps too.\"}, {\"start\": 434.52, \"end\": 435.88, \"text\": \"Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 435.88, \"end\": 437.12, \"text\": \"Your life.\"}, {\"start\": 437.12, \"end\": 440.4, \"text\": \"Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "f0-Who5qMr4": {
    "video_id": "f0-Who5qMr4",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.15.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180316",
    "duration": 575,
    "view_count": 839,
    "description": "3.15.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY’S HEADLINES:\n-Deaf literacy bill passes in Georgia\n-Multiple fatalities in Miami bridge collapse\n-Cocaine extortion led to ESPN exit\n-Minor league player beats up girlfriend, caught on camera\n-Activist and Councilwoman murdered in Brazil\n-Light it up and work it out!\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.88, \"end\": 9.4, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 9.4, \"end\": 11.62, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 11.62, \"end\": 13.4, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 13.4, \"end\": 16.1, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.84, \"end\": 22.78, \"text\": \"Big news for Georgia's deaf community!\"}, {\"start\": 22.94, \"end\": 33.62, \"text\": \"Today lawmakers passed House Bill 844 by a unanimous vote, 49-0.\"}, {\"start\": 33.62, \"end\": 42.58, \"text\": \"HB 844 is called \\\"Georgia Pathway.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 42.58, \"end\": 52.1, \"text\": \"The bill monitors the state's Deaf and hard of hearing children, their language acquisition,\"}, {\"start\": 52.1, \"end\": 55.62, \"text\": \"development and literacy.\"}, {\"start\": 55.62, \"end\": 63.06, \"text\": \"The bill involved three agencies who work with Deaf and hard of hearing children, plus\"}, {\"start\": 63.06, \"end\": 65.36, \"text\": \"other disabilities.\"}, {\"start\": 65.36, \"end\": 74.14, \"text\": \"They wanted to pool all of their resources so everyone was working towards the same goal,\"}, {\"start\": 74.14, \"end\": 79.5, \"text\": \"making sure no children fall through the cracks.\"}, {\"start\": 79.5, \"end\": 90.94, \"text\": \"Georgia representative Penny Houston and Senator P.K. Martin also provided support\"}, {\"start\": 90.94, \"end\": 94.34, \"text\": \"in passing the bill.\"}, {\"start\": 94.34, \"end\": 99.6, \"text\": \"Now the bill moves to the governor's office for the final approval.\"}, {\"start\": 102.68, \"end\": 110.96, \"text\": \"Just after the lunch hour today a pedestrian bridge collapsed in Miami.\"}, {\"start\": 110.96, \"end\": 120.4, \"text\": \"The bridge was at Florida International University over SW 8th St. connecting the campus to the\"}, {\"start\": 120.4, \"end\": 123.08, \"text\": \"student housing area.\"}, {\"start\": 123.08, \"end\": 132.1, \"text\": \"911 calls started pouring in about 1:30 PM.\"}, {\"start\": 132.1, \"end\": 138.42, \"text\": \"Officials say 8 cars were crushed underneath the 950 ton bridge.\"}, {\"start\": 138.42, \"end\": 140.76, \"text\": \"Several people were transported to hospitals.\"}, {\"start\": 140.76, \"end\": 146.36, \"text\": \"At this time police have not released how many people were killed.\"}, {\"start\": 146.36, \"end\": 152.88, \"text\": \"Officials say a police officer who owns a business across the street from the bridge\"}, {\"start\": 152.88, \"end\": 156.42, \"text\": \"was first on the scene and helped victims until others arrived.\"}, {\"start\": 156.42, \"end\": 160.8, \"text\": \"Several law enforcement agencies are assisting in the search and rescue effort, including\"}, {\"start\": 160.8, \"end\": 162.08, \"text\": \"rescue dogs.\"}, {\"start\": 162.08, \"end\": 166.72, \"text\": \"They say their primary goal is looking for survivors.\"}, {\"start\": 166.72, \"end\": 171.06, \"text\": \"Police ordered helicopters hovering over the scene to move away from the scene so they\"}, {\"start\": 171.08, \"end\": 174.46, \"text\": \"could hear the voices of any survivors.\"}, {\"start\": 174.46, \"end\": 178.86, \"text\": \"The bridge was just installed Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 178.86, \"end\": 185.24, \"text\": \"At this point investigators aren't sure what caused the collapse.\"}, {\"start\": 185.24, \"end\": 191.36, \"text\": \"Officials are asking people who normally drive in the area to stay away so investigators\"}, {\"start\": 191.36, \"end\": 193.06, \"text\": \"can work.\"}, {\"start\": 193.06, \"end\": 198.28, \"text\": \"Police also gave out a phone number for \\\"family members only\\\" who may be concerned about their\"}, {\"start\": 198.28, \"end\": 199.8, \"text\": \"loved ones.\"}, {\"start\": 199.8, \"end\": 207.3, \"text\": \"The number is 305-348-3481.\"}, {\"start\": 209.62, \"end\": 218.8, \"text\": \"Former ESPN president John Skipper has revealed to the \\\"Hollywood Reporter\\\" that he stepped\"}, {\"start\": 218.8, \"end\": 223.2, \"text\": \"down last year because of a cocaine extortion plot.\"}, {\"start\": 223.2, \"end\": 229.92, \"text\": \"Skipper said he had always been careful about his cocaine usage.\"}, {\"start\": 229.92, \"end\": 241.9, \"text\": \"The problem was his decision to buy from a new supplier.\"}, {\"start\": 241.92, \"end\": 252.28, \"text\": \"According to Skipper, that supplier threatened him and he believed his family and professional\"}, {\"start\": 252.28, \"end\": 255.6, \"text\": \"life were in danger.\"}, {\"start\": 255.6, \"end\": 266.58, \"text\": \"Skipper said he discussed the situation with Disney CEO Bob Iger and that Iger agreed Skipper\"}, {\"start\": 266.58, \"end\": 268.3, \"text\": \"should resign.\"}, {\"start\": 268.34, \"end\": 273.04, \"text\": \"ESPN provided no comment on the story.\"}, {\"start\": 276.64, \"end\": 282.36, \"text\": \"We want to warn you: the video in this story is very disturbing.\"}, {\"start\": 282.36, \"end\": 296.7, \"text\": \"In 2016 professional baseball player Danny Vasquez was arrested on domestic violence\"}, {\"start\": 296.7, \"end\": 301.52, \"text\": \"charges after viciously beating his girlfriend.\"}, {\"start\": 301.52, \"end\": 304.52, \"text\": \"Video of the incident has just been released.\"}, {\"start\": 304.52, \"end\": 314.76, \"text\": \"It shows Vasquez punching the woman in the face and head multiple times and dragging\"}, {\"start\": 314.76, \"end\": 319.58, \"text\": \"her down a flight of steps by her hair.\"}, {\"start\": 319.6, \"end\": 324.04, \"text\": \"All the woman does is hold up her arms in self-defense.\"}, {\"start\": 324.04, \"end\": 333.42, \"text\": \"Vasquez was wearing his baseball uniform at the time and the video was recorded inside\"}, {\"start\": 333.42, \"end\": 338.54, \"text\": \"a baseball stadium in Corpus Christi, Texas, which indicates the incident took place before\"}, {\"start\": 338.54, \"end\": 342.16, \"text\": \"or after a game.\"}, {\"start\": 342.16, \"end\": 350.66, \"text\": \"Again, we want to warn you the video is graphic.\"}, {\"start\": 380.8, \"end\": 387.52, \"text\": \"Two days later the Houston Astros cut Vasquez from their minor league team.\"}, {\"start\": 387.52, \"end\": 393.92, \"text\": \"The woman refused to press charges so the case was dropped.\"}, {\"start\": 398.4, \"end\": 415.34, \"text\": \"Brazil is in a state of shock after a well-known activist and councilwoman was murdered last\"}, {\"start\": 415.46, \"end\": 416.9, \"text\": \"night.\"}, {\"start\": 416.92, \"end\": 426.26, \"text\": \"Marielle Franco was traveling in a car when she was shot to death.\"}, {\"start\": 426.26, \"end\": 428.86, \"text\": \"The driver was also killed.\"}, {\"start\": 428.86, \"end\": 434.84, \"text\": \"Authorities say this crime was carefully planned.\"}, {\"start\": 434.84, \"end\": 441.44, \"text\": \"The day before she was murdered, Franco complained about the violence in the city on her Twitter\"}, {\"start\": 441.44, \"end\": 452.62, \"text\": \"page and she called out the military police for the abuse taking place in Rio de Janeiro.\"}, {\"start\": 452.62, \"end\": 458.18, \"text\": \"The community she served is staging vigils in her memory and massive demonstrations are\"}, {\"start\": 458.18, \"end\": 463.26, \"text\": \"popping up in protest of her killing.\"}, {\"start\": 467.56, \"end\": 484.1, \"text\": \"Colorado fitness instructor Janessa Lea believes she operates the first marijuana-friendly\"}, {\"start\": 484.14, \"end\": 486.64, \"text\": \"fitness facility in the world.\"}, {\"start\": 486.64, \"end\": 497.62, \"text\": \"Her mantra: \\\"Light it up and work it out!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 497.62, \"end\": 504.04, \"text\": \"To be clear: the workout facility does not sell marijuana.\"}, {\"start\": 504.04, \"end\": 513.12, \"text\": \"Instead, Lea gives it to clients for free as samples.\"}, {\"start\": 513.12, \"end\": 522.6, \"text\": \"The gym is open to the public but you can't just walk in and take part.\"}, {\"start\": 522.6, \"end\": 534.6, \"text\": \"You have to request an invite via email and then provide registration information.\"}, {\"start\": 534.6, \"end\": 545.7, \"text\": \"Recreational marijuana is legal in Colorado and Lea says it should be an option for fitness too.\"}, {\"start\": 549.06, \"end\": 551.8, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 551.8, \"end\": 553.64, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 553.64, \"end\": 555.94, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 555.94, \"end\": 560.3, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 560.3, \"end\": 566.3, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "-_ojvPJp0c0": {
    "video_id": "-_ojvPJp0c0",
    "title": "Alcohol could help you live past 90 (ASL - 2.21.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180222",
    "duration": 84,
    "view_count": 195,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.08, \"end\": 13.84, \"text\": \"Dr. Claudia Kawas, a researcher from the University of California, says reaching for a wine glass\"}, {\"start\": 13.84, \"end\": 18.74, \"text\": \"rather than a dumbbell may help you live longer.\"}, {\"start\": 18.74, \"end\": 27.86, \"text\": \"Kawas studied 1,700 people who lived until at least 90 and found that the people who\"}, {\"start\": 27.86, \"end\": 35.18, \"text\": \"drank two glasses of wine or beer a night reduced their chances of dying prematurely\"}, {\"start\": 35.18, \"end\": 37.72, \"text\": \"by 18 percent.\"}, {\"start\": 37.72, \"end\": 49.88, \"text\": \"But before you cancel your gym membership, the study also found that 15 to 40 minutes\"}, {\"start\": 49.88, \"end\": 56.0, \"text\": \"of daily physical activity reduce the risk of early death by 11 percent.\"}, {\"start\": 56.0, \"end\": 66.02, \"text\": \"And people who spend two hours a day on a hobby are 21 percent less likely to die early.\"}, {\"start\": 66.02, \"end\": 74.38, \"text\": \"Dr. Kawas admits she does not know why modest drinking seems to help people live longer\"}, {\"start\": 74.38, \"end\": 82.24, \"text\": \"but she firmly believes it improves longevity.\"}]"
  },
  "uYYYIN5bDeY": {
    "video_id": "uYYYIN5bDeY",
    "title": "Sign1News 10.21.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171022",
    "duration": 456,
    "view_count": 166,
    "description": "October 21, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-TAMPA UNSOLVED HOMICIDES SURVEILLANCE VIDEO\n-TRUMP ALLOWS RELEASE OF CLASSIFIED JFK FILES\n-OPIOID COMMISSION MEETS BEFORE FINAL REPORT\n-BORDER WALL PROTOTYPES BEING CONSTRUCTED\n-SGT LA DAVID JOHNSON FUNERAL\n-U.S. DEFICIT HITS $666 BILLION\n-TAKE A WALK ON MARS IN YOUR OWN LIVING ROOM\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. W",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "en",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 7.0, \"end\": 12.0, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News. I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 12.0, \"end\": 16.0, \"text\": \"And here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.0, \"end\": 20.0, \"text\": \"In Tampa police need the public's help\"}, {\"start\": 21.0, \"end\": 26.0, \"text\": \"identifying this person. Take a good look.\"}, {\"start\": 26.0, \"end\": 31.0, \"text\": \"The video shows someone walking down a street. A man was\"}, {\"start\": 31.0, \"end\": 38.0, \"text\": \"shot and killed at a nearby bus stop.\"}, {\"start\": 38.0, \"end\": 41.0, \"text\": \"Police believe the person in the video\"}, {\"start\": 41.0, \"end\": 45.0, \"text\": \"may have seen something or could even be the shooter.\"}, {\"start\": 45.0, \"end\": 50.0, \"text\": \"And not just in the bus stop shooting but two\"}, {\"start\": 50.0, \"end\": 53.0, \"text\": \"other homicides.\"}, {\"start\": 53.0, \"end\": 57.0, \"text\": \"Police say all three killings are related although\"}, {\"start\": 58.0, \"end\": 63.0, \"text\": \"they are not using the word serial killer to describe the person they are looking for.\"}, {\"start\": 63.0, \"end\": 67.0, \"text\": \"But the chief of police did say until someone is caught\"}, {\"start\": 68.0, \"end\": 73.0, \"text\": \"everyone is a potential suspect.\"}, {\"start\": 76.0, \"end\": 80.0, \"text\": \"Today President Trump tweeted he's planning to\"}, {\"start\": 80.0, \"end\": 84.0, \"text\": \"authorize the release of the classified government\"}, {\"start\": 84.0, \"end\": 89.0, \"text\": \"documents regarding the 1963 assassination\"}, {\"start\": 90.0, \"end\": 94.0, \"text\": \"of President John F. Kennedy.\"}, {\"start\": 95.0, \"end\": 100.0, \"text\": \"Those documents could reveal new details\"}, {\"start\": 100.0, \"end\": 104.0, \"text\": \"about the assassination. A 1992 law\"}, {\"start\": 105.0, \"end\": 110.0, \"text\": \"known as the John F. Kennedy Assassination\"}, {\"start\": 110.0, \"end\": 114.0, \"text\": \"Records Collection Act requires more than\"}, {\"start\": 114.0, \"end\": 119.0, \"text\": \"3000 previously classified documents be\"}, {\"start\": 119.0, \"end\": 124.0, \"text\": \"made public by the law's 25th anniversary which\"}, {\"start\": 124.0, \"end\": 129.0, \"text\": \"is Thursday October 26.\"}, {\"start\": 129.0, \"end\": 134.0, \"text\": \"The President still has the power to withhold any or all\"}, {\"start\": 134.0, \"end\": 138.0, \"text\": \"documents he believes could pose harm to\"}, {\"start\": 138.0, \"end\": 143.0, \"text\": \"U.S. intelligence, law enforcement,\"}, {\"start\": 144.0, \"end\": 149.0, \"text\": \"the military or U.S. foreign relations. That is why\"}, {\"start\": 149.0, \"end\": 154.0, \"text\": \"some historians do not believe these documents will lead\"}, {\"start\": 154.0, \"end\": 158.0, \"text\": \"to any bombshell discovery in the Kennedy assassination.\"}, {\"start\": 162.0, \"end\": 167.0, \"text\": \"On Monday President Trump declared a national emergency\"}, {\"start\": 167.0, \"end\": 173.0, \"text\": \"to fight opioid overdoses.\"}, {\"start\": 173.0, \"end\": 178.0, \"text\": \"The number of American deaths involving opioids\"}, {\"start\": 178.0, \"end\": 181.0, \"text\": \"has quadrupled since 1999.\"}, {\"start\": 181.0, \"end\": 185.0, \"text\": \"Opioids are a group of drugs that include\"}, {\"start\": 185.0, \"end\": 192.0, \"text\": \"heroin and painkillers like oxycodone,\"}, {\"start\": 192.0, \"end\": 197.0, \"text\": \"codeine and morphine.\"}, {\"start\": 197.0, \"end\": 202.0, \"text\": \"President Trump has formed a commission to discuss\"}, {\"start\": 202.0, \"end\": 207.0, \"text\": \"insurance related issues and come up with ideas\"}, {\"start\": 207.0, \"end\": 212.0, \"text\": \"that could help state and federal agencies have more resources\"}, {\"start\": 212.0, \"end\": 217.0, \"text\": \"in fighting the epidemic.\"}, {\"start\": 219.3, \"end\": 223.0, \"text\": \"When President Trump took office he said\"}, {\"start\": 223.0, \"end\": 227.0, \"text\": \"he was going to build walls along the border\"}, {\"start\": 227.0, \"end\": 231.0, \"text\": \"to prevent people from crossing into the United States illegally.\"}, {\"start\": 231.0, \"end\": 235.0, \"text\": \"Well take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 235.0, \"end\": 239.0, \"text\": \"These are prototypes of what the wall could look like. They are being built\"}, {\"start\": 239.0, \"end\": 245.0, \"text\": \"in a remote area outside of San Diego, California.\"}, {\"start\": 245.0, \"end\": 250.0, \"text\": \"Construction companies from all around the country are\"}, {\"start\": 250.0, \"end\": 254.0, \"text\": \"submitting their designs for what the wall could look like.\"}, {\"start\": 254.0, \"end\": 259.0, \"text\": \"All of the walls are about\"}, {\"start\": 259.0, \"end\": 263.0, \"text\": \"thirty feet high to keep people from jumping over them.\"}, {\"start\": 263.0, \"end\": 268.0, \"text\": \"Some have deep concrete bottoms\"}, {\"start\": 268.0, \"end\": 273.0, \"text\": \"to prevent people from tunneling underneath.\"}, {\"start\": 273.0, \"end\": 278.0, \"text\": \"Others have razor-sharp barbed wire on the top.\"}, {\"start\": 278.0, \"end\": 283.0, \"text\": \"The price tag for all of the walls\"}, {\"start\": 283.0, \"end\": 287.0, \"text\": \"is about 20 million dollars.\"}, {\"start\": 288.0, \"end\": 293.0, \"text\": \"Today in Cooper City, Florida a private\"}, {\"start\": 293.0, \"end\": 298.0, \"text\": \"funeral was held for Sergeant La David\"}, {\"start\": 298.0, \"end\": 303.0, \"text\": \"Johnson. Johnson was one of\"}, {\"start\": 303.0, \"end\": 307.0, \"text\": \"four U.S. soldiers killed in an ISIS\"}, {\"start\": 307.0, \"end\": 312.0, \"text\": \"ambush in Niger, Africa earlier this month.\"}, {\"start\": 312.0, \"end\": 317.0, \"text\": \"The incident is under investigation, including how\"}, {\"start\": 317.0, \"end\": 324.0, \"text\": \"Johnson's body got left behind when the rescue helicopter showed up.\"}, {\"start\": 324.0, \"end\": 331.0, \"text\": \"His remains were discovered a mile from the ambush site.\"}, {\"start\": 334.0, \"end\": 337.0, \"text\": \"The federal deficit has reached a\"}, {\"start\": 337.0, \"end\": 341.0, \"text\": \"sky high 666-billion dollars. But the Congressional\"}, {\"start\": 342.0, \"end\": 348.0, \"text\": \"Budget Office says that number is right in line with what they estimated it would be.\"}, {\"start\": 349.0, \"end\": 353.0, \"text\": \"It's also $80 billion more than last year\"}, {\"start\": 353.0, \"end\": 358.0, \"text\": \"and the largest federal deficit since 2013.\"}, {\"start\": 360.0, \"end\": 364.0, \"text\": \"Some government officials say weak\"}, {\"start\": 364.0, \"end\": 369.0, \"text\": \"economic growth is to blame. Others say the government needs\"}, {\"start\": 369.0, \"end\": 375.0, \"text\": \"to be smarter when it comes to spending and tax reform.\"}, {\"start\": 377.001, \"end\": 380.001, \"text\": \"NASA and Google are teaming up\"}, {\"start\": 380.1, \"end\": 385.1, \"text\": \"to offer free virtual space exploration.\"}, {\"start\": 386.0, \"end\": 393.0, \"text\": \"Access Mars was released earlier this week.\"}, {\"start\": 394.0, \"end\": 397.0, \"text\": \"The technology transports\"}, {\"start\": 397.0, \"end\": 402.0, \"text\": \"users to Mars from anywhere.\"}, {\"start\": 402.0, \"end\": 407.0, \"text\": \"It simulates walking on Mars and provides closeup views\"}, {\"start\": 408.0, \"end\": 412.0, \"text\": \"of discoveries made by the Curiosity rover.\"}, {\"start\": 412.0, \"end\": 418.0, \"text\": \"You can view it on a computer, phone or through a\"}, {\"start\": 418.0, \"end\": 422.0, \"text\": \"virtual reality headset. For more information go to\"}, {\"start\": 424.0, \"end\": 428.0, \"text\": \"AccessMars.com.\"}, {\"start\": 430.0, \"end\": 433.0, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 433.0, \"end\": 437.0, \"text\": \"I am Jethro Wooddall. Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 437.0, \"end\": 442.0, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 442.0, \"end\": 449.0, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "OClHG2EYscM": {
    "video_id": "OClHG2EYscM",
    "title": "Sign1News 1.22.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180123",
    "duration": 528,
    "view_count": 2224,
    "description": "1.22.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Senate reaches compromise to end government shutdown\n-USA Gymnastics board members resign\n-Pope apologizes for sex abuse comments\n-Boy with 10 LB tumor on face dies after surgery\n-Gender neutral kids items hit store shelves\n-SAG Awards recap\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Languag",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 8.08, \"end\": 8.84, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 8.84, \"end\": 10.64, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.64, \"end\": 11.56, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 11.56, \"end\": 14.84, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 17.62, \"end\": 27.64, \"text\": \"The stalemate over government funding has finally been broken with the Senate voting\"}, {\"start\": 27.64, \"end\": 32.56, \"text\": \"today on a compromise, ending the government shutdown after two days.\"}, {\"start\": 32.58, \"end\": 38.94, \"text\": \"A vote to fund the government through February 8 overwhelmingly passed the Senate Monday\"}, {\"start\": 38.94, \"end\": 40.72, \"text\": \"afternoon.\"}, {\"start\": 40.72, \"end\": 56.86, \"text\": \"Democrats gave GOP leader Mitch McConnell the support needed to reach the necessary\"}, {\"start\": 56.86, \"end\": 58.28, \"text\": \"60 votes.\"}, {\"start\": 58.36, \"end\": 67.3, \"text\": \"In the end, Democrats hope that McConnell will keep his word and hold a vote on DACA\"}, {\"start\": 67.3, \"end\": 69.48, \"text\": \"before February 8th.\"}, {\"start\": 69.48, \"end\": 81.0, \"text\": \"Republican Senator Lindsey Graham is confident a deal can be reached.\"}, {\"start\": 81.0, \"end\": 88.96, \"text\": \"As for President Trump, aides say behind the scenes he's been talking with Republican leaders\"}, {\"start\": 88.96, \"end\": 94.3, \"text\": \"but he mostly left negotiating up to the Senate and members of his staff.\"}, {\"start\": 96.78, \"end\": 108.2, \"text\": \"Today officials with USA gymnastics tweeted that chairman Paul Parilla, Vice Chairman\"}, {\"start\": 108.32, \"end\": 115.6, \"text\": \"Jay Binder and Treasurer Bitsy Kelly tendered their resignations effective January 21, 2018.\"}, {\"start\": 115.84, \"end\": 121.84, \"text\": \"The resignations are as a result of intense public criticism over how the organization\"}, {\"start\": 121.84, \"end\": 133.76, \"text\": \"responded to accusations that team doctor Larry Nassar sexually abused hundreds of young\"}, {\"start\": 133.76, \"end\": 136.64, \"text\": \"girls.\"}, {\"start\": 136.64, \"end\": 147.12, \"text\": \"Day five of Nassar's sentencing hearing continued today in Michigan.\"}, {\"start\": 147.28, \"end\": 152.08, \"text\": \"More than 90 women already confronted Nassar last week.\"}, {\"start\": 152.08, \"end\": 160.56, \"text\": \"About 30 more victims are expected to make impact statements which could last into Tuesday.\"}, {\"start\": 160.56, \"end\": 166.56, \"text\": \"Nassar, who also worked at Michigan State University, has already pleaded guilty to\"}, {\"start\": 166.56, \"end\": 172.72, \"text\": \"seven counts of criminal sexual conduct.\"}, {\"start\": 172.88, \"end\": 180.64, \"text\": \"He also admitted to sexually assaulting and abusing women and young girls under the pretense\"}, {\"start\": 180.64, \"end\": 183.92, \"text\": \"of medical treatment.\"}, {\"start\": 183.92, \"end\": 194.4, \"text\": \"Nassar has already been sentenced to 60 years in prison on federal child pornography charges.\"}, {\"start\": 196.48, \"end\": 202.08, \"text\": \"Pope Francis is apologizing for comments that critics say demean victims of sexual abuse.\"}, {\"start\": 202.08, \"end\": 209.28, \"text\": \"The Pope told a reporter last week in Chile that accusations of sex abuse without proof\"}, {\"start\": 209.28, \"end\": 211.28, \"text\": \"are slander.\"}, {\"start\": 211.28, \"end\": 218.88, \"text\": \"Pope Francis was discussing Chilean Bishop Juan Barros, who has been accused of covering\"}, {\"start\": 218.88, \"end\": 222.24, \"text\": \"up sex abuse by a fellow priests.\"}, {\"start\": 222.24, \"end\": 232.88, \"text\": \"Bishop Barros denies the allegations but a Catholic news agency says the Vatican found\"}, {\"start\": 232.88, \"end\": 241.52, \"text\": \"the accused priest guilty of sexual abuse in 2011.\"}, {\"start\": 241.52, \"end\": 244.08, \"text\": \"Pope Francis apologized for his words saying he did not intend to hurt the victims of sexual\"}, {\"start\": 244.08, \"end\": 245.84, \"text\": \"abuse.\"}, {\"start\": 245.84, \"end\": 251.92, \"text\": \"But he also emphasized that there is no evidence that Bishop Barros did anything wrong.\"}, {\"start\": 254.32, \"end\": 260.64, \"text\": \"Emanuel Zayas has died.\"}, {\"start\": 260.64, \"end\": 268.96, \"text\": \"He was the 14-year-old Cuban boy who had a basketball-sized tumor on his face.\"}, {\"start\": 268.96, \"end\": 274.68, \"text\": \"His family brought him to Miami because it was difficult for Cuban doctors to remove\"}, {\"start\": 274.68, \"end\": 279.0, \"text\": \"the 10 pound tumor.\"}, {\"start\": 279.0, \"end\": 288.28, \"text\": \"But Miami doctors say after removing the tumor, Emanuel developed kidney and liver complications.\"}, {\"start\": 288.28, \"end\": 294.88, \"text\": \"His doctors and family members say he died Friday night as a result of those complications.\"}, {\"start\": 294.88, \"end\": 301.38, \"text\": \"Emanuel's remains were donated to science so doctors can study his rare condition called\"}, {\"start\": 301.38, \"end\": 314.12, \"text\": \"polyostotic fibrous dysplasia.\"}, {\"start\": 316.76, \"end\": 324.94, \"text\": \"Many clothing brands have decided to offer gender-neutral options for clothing to attract\"}, {\"start\": 324.94, \"end\": 329.74, \"text\": \"a more diverse clientele.\"}, {\"start\": 329.74, \"end\": 337.7, \"text\": \"Instead of seeing a shirt listed as being for a boy or girl, now you will see it as\"}, {\"start\": 337.7, \"end\": 343.9, \"text\": \"a kid shirt or unisex.\"}, {\"start\": 343.9, \"end\": 352.98, \"text\": \"Abercrombie and Finch's line features 25 styles.\"}, {\"start\": 352.98, \"end\": 358.88, \"text\": \"The sizes are the same regardless of the gender.\"}, {\"start\": 358.88, \"end\": 365.66, \"text\": \"And it's created for kids ages 5 to 14.\"}, {\"start\": 365.66, \"end\": 371.42, \"text\": \"H&amp;M has a unisex demin collection for adults.\"}, {\"start\": 371.42, \"end\": 376.82, \"text\": \"And Target dropped references to boys and girls in the toy, home and entertainment aisles.\"}, {\"start\": 376.82, \"end\": 384.96, \"text\": \"You won't see boys toys -- instead aisles are labeled action figures or dolls.\"}, {\"start\": 384.96, \"end\": 392.48, \"text\": \"Retail experts say the trend benefits shoppers who want to buy an item for child without\"}, {\"start\": 392.48, \"end\": 399.68, \"text\": \"feeling restricted by labels.\"}, {\"start\": 402.24, \"end\": 409.96, \"text\": \"Hundreds of Hollywood stars turned out for the 24th annual Screen Actors Guild (SAG)\"}, {\"start\": 409.96, \"end\": 414.32, \"text\": \"awards in Los Angeles last night.\"}, {\"start\": 414.32, \"end\": 418.4, \"text\": \"Here's a quick recap of some of the night's big winners:\"}, {\"start\": 418.4, \"end\": 427.76, \"text\": \"The movie \\\"Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri\\\" won four awards, including Outstanding\"}, {\"start\": 427.76, \"end\": 432.76, \"text\": \"Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture.\"}, {\"start\": 432.76, \"end\": 440.8, \"text\": \"Nicole Kidman won her first SAG award for Outstanding Performance by a Female Actor\"}, {\"start\": 440.8, \"end\": 448.32, \"text\": \"in a Mini-Series or T-V movie for \\\"Big Little Lies.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 448.32, \"end\": 461.02, \"text\": \"Alexander Skarsgard won for Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor for \\\"Big Little Lies.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 461.06, \"end\": 468.62, \"text\": \"Outstanding Performance by an Ensemble in a TV Drama series went to the cast of \\\"This\"}, {\"start\": 468.62, \"end\": 470.08, \"text\": \"Is Us.\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 470.08, \"end\": 481.72, \"text\": \"\\\"This Is Us\\\" star Sterling K. Brown became the first African-American to win a SAG award\"}, {\"start\": 481.72, \"end\": 485.28, \"text\": \"for Outstanding Performance by Male Actor in a Drama Series.\"}, {\"start\": 485.28, \"end\": 496.0, \"text\": \"And legendary actor Morgan Freeman was awarded a Lifetime Achievement award, one of the highest\"}, {\"start\": 496.0, \"end\": 503.08, \"text\": \"honors in the entertainment industry.\"}, {\"start\": 505.64, \"end\": 507.68, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 507.68, \"end\": 508.94, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 508.94, \"end\": 510.8, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 510.8, \"end\": 514.64, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 514.64, \"end\": 519.52, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "WRs8bBaxCZM": {
    "video_id": "WRs8bBaxCZM",
    "title": "Sign1News 2.11.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180212",
    "duration": 426,
    "view_count": 918,
    "description": "2.11.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).  \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Five stabbed in church attack\n-Sheriff heard on recording saying “take him out!”\n-Senator seeks records on Trump’s mansion Russian sale\n-Equifax hack could be worse than thought\n-Pyeongchang naked marathon\n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.8, \"end\": 7.76, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 7.76, \"end\": 10.04, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 10.04, \"end\": 11.42, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 11.42, \"end\": 14.48, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 18.04, \"end\": 30.64, \"text\": \"An attacker went on a stabbing spree with the sword during morning mass Sunday in Indonesia.\"}, {\"start\": 30.64, \"end\": 37.9, \"text\": \"Church security tried to prevent the man from entering the church but he fought his way\"}, {\"start\": 37.9, \"end\": 42.78, \"text\": \"in and started attacking during the middle of prayer.\"}, {\"start\": 42.78, \"end\": 44.46, \"text\": \"Five men were injured.\"}, {\"start\": 44.46, \"end\": 54.52, \"text\": \"Cell phone video shows the man after the attack, shouting and angrily waving the sword around.\"}, {\"start\": 54.52, \"end\": 56.72, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 69.12, \"end\": 78.08, \"text\": \"According to CNN Indonesia one of the men injured was the pastor of the church.\"}, {\"start\": 78.08, \"end\": 84.8, \"text\": \"The attacker also slashed the statues of Jesus and Mary.\"}, {\"start\": 84.8, \"end\": 90.4, \"text\": \"The attack didn't stop until police shot the attacker in the stomach.\"}, {\"start\": 90.4, \"end\": 95.04, \"text\": \"He was taken to the hospital for treatment and interrogation.\"}, {\"start\": 97.76, \"end\": 109.6, \"text\": \"Last April, officers attempted to pull over a 33-year-old white male named Michael Dial.\"}, {\"start\": 109.6, \"end\": 114.4, \"text\": \"This is video of the chase.\"}, {\"start\": 114.4, \"end\": 117.92, \"text\": \"They suspected him of driving with a suspended license.\"}, {\"start\": 117.92, \"end\": 120.0, \"text\": \"But he kept on driving.\"}, {\"start\": 120.0, \"end\": 121.92, \"text\": \"This was not a high-speed chase.\"}, {\"start\": 121.92, \"end\": 124.96, \"text\": \"Officers say they never went faster than 50 miles per hour.\"}, {\"start\": 124.96, \"end\": 130.4, \"text\": \"Eventually they used a pit maneuver to force Dial's truck off the road.\"}, {\"start\": 130.72, \"end\": 137.92, \"text\": \"Witnesses say Dial never posed a threat to the public, but orders came from White County\"}, {\"start\": 137.92, \"end\": 148.48, \"text\": \"Sheriff Oddie Shoupe over the radio to \\\"take him out\\\" by any means necessary, including\"}, {\"start\": 148.48, \"end\": 151.84, \"text\": \"deadly force.\"}, {\"start\": 151.84, \"end\": 155.04, \"text\": \"About a minute later shots were fired and Dial was killed.\"}, {\"start\": 155.04, \"end\": 160.0, \"text\": \"Shoupe was not involved in the chase and he didn't see any danger Dial may or may not\"}, {\"start\": 160.0, \"end\": 161.64, \"text\": \"have presented.\"}, {\"start\": 161.64, \"end\": 169.28, \"text\": \"But when Shoupe arrived on the scene later, one of the officer's body cams was left on\"}, {\"start\": 169.28, \"end\": 173.28, \"text\": \"and, unbeknownst to Shoupe, he was recorded saying this:\"}, {\"start\": 189.76, \"end\": 194.56, \"text\": \"Shoupe seems to suggest he would rather his officers shoot and kill Dial rather than damage\"}, {\"start\": 194.56, \"end\": 199.04, \"text\": \"their patrol cars.\"}, {\"start\": 199.04, \"end\": 204.32, \"text\": \"The district attorney ruled the shooting justified.\"}, {\"start\": 204.32, \"end\": 211.84, \"text\": \"But Dial's widow has filed a federal lawsuit against the parties involved.\"}, {\"start\": 214.88, \"end\": 229.76, \"text\": \"Democratic Senator Ron Wyden from Oregon wants to see records of President Trump's sale of\"}, {\"start\": 229.76, \"end\": 232.8, \"text\": \"a mansion in Florida.\"}, {\"start\": 232.8, \"end\": 234.88, \"text\": \"Wyden is a high-ranking member of the Finance Committee.\"}, {\"start\": 234.88, \"end\": 246.56, \"text\": \"He says lawmakers want to look for potential money laundering and other financial deals\"}, {\"start\": 246.56, \"end\": 248.48, \"text\": \"with Russia.\"}, {\"start\": 248.48, \"end\": 264.0, \"text\": \"Trump sold the house in Palm Beach to Russian billionaire Dmitry Rybolovev in 2008.\"}, {\"start\": 264.0, \"end\": 274.24, \"text\": \"Trump made more than $40 million in the transaction but Wyden says $40 million is more than three\"}, {\"start\": 274.24, \"end\": 276.64, \"text\": \"times the value of the estate.\"}, {\"start\": 276.64, \"end\": 281.44, \"text\": \"Trump said that he never met Rybolovev.\"}, {\"start\": 285.12, \"end\": 295.68, \"text\": \"Last year hackers broke into credit bureau company Equifax and stole the personal information\"}, {\"start\": 295.68, \"end\": 297.8, \"text\": \"of 145 million customers.\"}, {\"start\": 297.8, \"end\": 301.72, \"text\": \"The breach happened between May and July 2017.\"}, {\"start\": 301.72, \"end\": 308.88, \"text\": \"Now there are fears the massive breach at credit bureau compay may be worse than first thought.\"}, {\"start\": 308.94, \"end\": 316.64, \"text\": \"According to confidential documents Equifax provided to the Senate banking committee,\"}, {\"start\": 316.64, \"end\": 321.28, \"text\": \"information such as tax IDs and drivers license details may have been accessed by hackers,\"}, {\"start\": 321.28, \"end\": 326.08, \"text\": \"in addition to other personal information like names, social security numbers and home\"}, {\"start\": 326.08, \"end\": 328.32, \"text\": \"addresses.\"}, {\"start\": 328.32, \"end\": 336.32, \"text\": \"Federal agencies, state officials and lawmakers are currently probing Equifax.\"}, {\"start\": 339.04, \"end\": 360.16, \"text\": \"South Koreans held the 26th annual \\\"Naked Marathon\\\" in Pyeongchang over the weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 360.16, \"end\": 369.28, \"text\": \"Around 1,800 people turned out for the event, despite temperatures hovering around 20 degrees.\"}, {\"start\": 369.28, \"end\": 378.08, \"text\": \"To qualify for the medal, you had to run shirtless and either sprint for 5 km or push harder\"}, {\"start\": 378.08, \"end\": 380.64, \"text\": \"for the 10K race.\"}, {\"start\": 380.64, \"end\": 386.72, \"text\": \"Gusting winds forced the Olympics to postpone the alpine ski competition.\"}, {\"start\": 386.72, \"end\": 392.96, \"text\": \"But bone chilling temperatures couldn't stop these Korean runners from this annual demonstration\"}, {\"start\": 392.96, \"end\": 395.52, \"text\": \"of winter madness.\"}, {\"start\": 398.4, \"end\": 400.8, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 400.8, \"end\": 402.72, \"text\": \"I'm Crystal Cousineau.\"}, {\"start\": 402.72, \"end\": 405.6, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 405.6, \"end\": 411.36, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 411.36, \"end\": 418.4, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "gjauzzsnOvI": {
    "video_id": "gjauzzsnOvI",
    "title": "Sign1News 11.26.17 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20171127",
    "duration": 447,
    "view_count": 251,
    "description": "November 26, 2017 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-JOHN CONYERS STEPS DOWN AMID SEXUAL HARASSMENT PROBE\n-NICARAGUA WOMEN'S MARCH BLOCKED\n-VACCINES ARRIVE IN YEMEN\n-VAN TRIES TO CUT INTO TRUMP MOTORCADE\n-CYBER MONDAY BEGINS SUNDAY\n-ACTRESS NAYA RIVERA ARRESTED\n-MARIAH CAREY POSTPONES CHRISTMAS TOUR\n-WEEKEND BOX OFFICE\n\nTHE SIGN1NEWS DIFFERENCE \nOur talented staff works hard each day to deliver quality news to you. We have backgrou",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 6.06, \"end\": 8.72, \"text\": \"Hello everyone. Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 8.72, \"end\": 14.2, \"text\": \"I'm Jethro Wooddall. Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 14.28, \"end\": 21.36, \"text\": \"Democratic House Representative John Conyers has stepped down as the second most senior\"}, {\"start\": 21.36, \"end\": 25.5, \"text\": \"member of the House Judiciary Committee.\"}, {\"start\": 25.5, \"end\": 29.18, \"text\": \"This decision comes after several former staff members\"}, {\"start\": 29.18, \"end\": 33.9, \"text\": \"accused Conyers of a variety of workplace abuses.\"}, {\"start\": 33.9, \"end\": 37.98, \"text\": \"He has been accused of requesting sexual favors,\"}, {\"start\": 37.98, \"end\": 43.0, \"text\": \"inappropriate touching and asking staff members\"}, {\"start\": 43.0, \"end\": 50.28, \"text\": \"to provide transportation for the women they suspected he was having an affair with.\"}, {\"start\": 50.28, \"end\": 50.78, \"text\": \"Conyers has expressly and vehemently denied any wrongdoing.\"}, {\"start\": 50.78, \"end\": 62.12, \"text\": \"As a result of the allegations, Conyers now faces a House Ethics Committee probe.\"}, {\"start\": 63.72, \"end\": 74.22, \"text\": \"A protest on violence against women was held in Managua, Nicaragua today.\"}, {\"start\": 74.22, \"end\": 80.36, \"text\": \"But when the group reached one of the main streets in Managua, the police blocked the march.\"}, {\"start\": 80.44, \"end\": 86.84, \"text\": \"Other organizations from other parts of the country were there to support the women.\"}, {\"start\": 86.84, \"end\": 89.24, \"text\": \"But they were blocked also.\"}, {\"start\": 89.24, \"end\": 92.28, \"text\": \"No response from the government was given\"}, {\"start\": 92.28, \"end\": 96.22, \"text\": \"as to why the police did not allow the groups to pass.\"}, {\"start\": 97.92, \"end\": 104.46, \"text\": \"Critically needed aid arrived in Yemen on Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 104.46, \"end\": 113.16, \"text\": \"Several planes landed in Sanna carrying nearly 2 million vaccine doses,\"}, {\"start\": 113.16, \"end\": 116.5, \"text\": \"enough for 600,000 children.\"}, {\"start\": 116.5, \"end\": 127.04, \"text\": \"According to the United Nation's World Food program the vaccines were sent to protect\"}, {\"start\": 127.06, \"end\": 137.52, \"text\": \"against deadly diseases – – like pneumonia, tuberculosis and meningitis.\"}, {\"start\": 137.52, \"end\": 144.24, \"text\": \"This is the first such aid to arrive since Saudi Arabia imposed a blockade of the country\"}, {\"start\": 144.24, \"end\": 146.32, \"text\": \"in early November.\"}, {\"start\": 146.32, \"end\": 151.26, \"text\": \"A ship carrying wheat flour is also expected to arrive.\"}, {\"start\": 151.38, \"end\": 160.68, \"text\": \"According to the UN, around 7 million Yemenis are suffering from severe famine.\"}, {\"start\": 162.68, \"end\": 167.7, \"text\": \"As president Trump was on his way back from from Trump international golf club in\"}, {\"start\": 167.76, \"end\": 179.82, \"text\": \"West Palm Beach, Florida, a driver in a red van tried to cut into his motorcade on Saturday.\"}, {\"start\": 179.94, \"end\": 184.98, \"text\": \"Reporters who were following the motorcade caught the incident on camera.\"}, {\"start\": 184.98, \"end\": 188.3, \"text\": \"Reporters say when law enforcement stopped the van\"}, {\"start\": 188.3, \"end\": 194.76, \"text\": \"the driver made some obscene gestures.\"}, {\"start\": 194.78, \"end\": 197.38, \"text\": \"But nothing else happened.\"}, {\"start\": 197.46, \"end\": 201.8, \"text\": \"The president made it back to Mar-A-Lago safely.\"}, {\"start\": 203.96, \"end\": 208.24, \"text\": \"If you're not into the pushing and shoving of\"}, {\"start\": 208.26, \"end\": 212.62, \"text\": \"Black Friday sales, Cyber Monday is perfect for you.\"}, {\"start\": 212.62, \"end\": 219.18, \"text\": \"You never have to leave home during the busiest online shopping day of the year.\"}, {\"start\": 219.18, \"end\": 229.36, \"text\": \"But according to Retail-Me-Not.com Black Friday and Cyber Monday are starting to merge.\"}, {\"start\": 229.36, \"end\": 234.96, \"text\": \"Instead of Black Friday having its own day and Cyber Monday having a day of its own,\"}, {\"start\": 234.96, \"end\": 241.28, \"text\": \"it's now become Cyber week -- or five days of savings.\"}, {\"start\": 241.28, \"end\": 249.92, \"text\": \"According to Adobe Digital – – American shoppers spent a record $5 billion online\"}, {\"start\": 249.92, \"end\": 255.12, \"text\": \"on Black Friday – – almost 70% more than last year.\"}, {\"start\": 255.2, \"end\": 260.88, \"text\": \"So if you have to work Monday and can't surf the web for the best online deals -- don't worry.\"}, {\"start\": 260.88, \"end\": 267.2, \"text\": \"You can save online today, Tuesday or even as late as Thursday or Friday.\"}, {\"start\": 270.08, \"end\": 279.36, \"text\": \"\\\"Glee\\\" actress and singer Naya Rivera was arrested in West Virginia.\"}, {\"start\": 279.44, \"end\": 283.84, \"text\": \"She is facing a domestic battery charge.\"}, {\"start\": 283.84, \"end\": 289.2, \"text\": \"She was arrested and jailed just after midnight\"}, {\"start\": 289.2, \"end\": 292.08, \"text\": \"this morning but the judge released her on bond.\"}, {\"start\": 292.24, \"end\": 299.92, \"text\": \"According to the criminal complaint, Rivera's husband – – Ryan Dorsey – said she hit\"}, {\"start\": 299.92, \"end\": 309.84, \"text\": \"him in the head and lip while they were taking their two-year-old son for a walk.\"}, {\"start\": 309.92, \"end\": 314.24, \"text\": \"Cell phone video of the alleged assault led to the arrest.\"}, {\"start\": 314.24, \"end\": 319.52, \"text\": \"Rivera and Dorsey got married in 2014.\"}, {\"start\": 319.52, \"end\": 326.8, \"text\": \"Rivera filed for divorce from the actor in 2016 but called off their separation last month.\"}, {\"start\": 329.6, \"end\": 335.92, \"text\": \"Singer Mariah Carey is scrapping three more shows from her upcoming Christmas tour.\"}, {\"start\": 335.92, \"end\": 341.84, \"text\": \"The three canceled shows were originally scheduled for Monday, Tuesday and Friday next week.\"}, {\"start\": 342.08, \"end\": 345.28, \"text\": \"She says her doctors recommended a few extra\"}, {\"start\": 345.28, \"end\": 352.96, \"text\": \"days of rest, so she can recover from a respiratory infection.\"}, {\"start\": 352.96, \"end\": 356.16, \"text\": \"But Carey said on Instagram that she will\"}, {\"start\": 356.16, \"end\": 360.16, \"text\": \"resume the tour in New York on December 2.\"}, {\"start\": 360.16, \"end\": 365.84, \"text\": \"Her shows will then continue in Europe and Las Vegas.\"}, {\"start\": 368.48, \"end\": 372.0, \"text\": \"Here's a quick recap of this weekend's box office.\"}, {\"start\": 372.0, \"end\": 377.6, \"text\": \"Disney Pixar's \\\"Coco\\\" won the box office this holiday weekend.\"}, {\"start\": 377.6, \"end\": 383.36, \"text\": \"It took in just over $71 million in North America between Wednesday and Sunday.\"}, {\"start\": 383.36, \"end\": 387.68, \"text\": \"The flick is about a little boy who dreams of becoming a musician\"}, {\"start\": 387.68, \"end\": 393.6, \"text\": \"and is based on Mexican \\\"Day of the Dead\\\" traditions.\"}, {\"start\": 393.6, \"end\": 398.4, \"text\": \"\\\"Justice League\\\" took the number two spot\"}, {\"start\": 398.4, \"end\": 404.0, \"text\": \"making about $60 million in the US over its second weekend of release.\"}, {\"start\": 404.48, \"end\": 412.48, \"text\": \"And the family drama \\\"Wonder\\\" came in third place with about $32 million.\"}, {\"start\": 412.64, \"end\": 417.6, \"text\": \"It's taken in more than $69 million since its release,\"}, {\"start\": 417.76, \"end\": 423.2, \"text\": \"more than tripling its $20 million budget.\"}, {\"start\": 424.96, \"end\": 427.52, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 427.52, \"end\": 428.96, \"text\": \"I am Jethro Wooddall.\"}, {\"start\": 428.96, \"end\": 430.72, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 430.72, \"end\": 434.72, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 434.72, \"end\": 440.64, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "9eEZwzUZejY": {
    "video_id": "9eEZwzUZejY",
    "title": "Sign1News 3.9.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL).",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180309",
    "duration": 473,
    "view_count": 1134,
    "description": "3.9.18 - News for the deaf community powered by CNN in American Sign Language (ASL). \n\nTODAY'S HEADLINES:\n-Florida school shooter withdraws guilty plea\n-Woman stops car thief with kid inside\n-State Dept warns spring breakers of Mexico threat\n-Hospitals offer big benefits to recruit nurses\n-Russians release anti-Hillary Clinton video game\n-Curious penguins find camera, take selfie video \n\nSign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news ",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 9.08, \"end\": 10.92, \"text\": \"Hello everyone.\"}, {\"start\": 10.92, \"end\": 13.28, \"text\": \"Welcome to Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 13.28, \"end\": 14.8, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 14.8, \"end\": 17.72, \"text\": \"Here are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 19.9, \"end\": 27.5, \"text\": \"Florida school shooter Nikolas Cruz made a court appearance earlier this week.\"}, {\"start\": 27.5, \"end\": 34.56, \"text\": \"Initially Cruz's lawyer said he was going to enter a guilty plea in order to avoid the\"}, {\"start\": 34.56, \"end\": 37.16, \"text\": \"death penalty.\"}, {\"start\": 37.16, \"end\": 54.54, \"text\": \"Instead he withdrew his not guilty plea and is now refusing to enter a plea at all.\"}, {\"start\": 54.54, \"end\": 64.1, \"text\": \"If Cruz continues to refuse to speak, a judge can enter a plea for him during his arraignment\"}, {\"start\": 64.1, \"end\": 68.54, \"text\": \"hearing, which is set for next Wednesday, March 14.\"}, {\"start\": 68.54, \"end\": 77.34, \"text\": \"That's exactly one month after the shooting at Marjory Stoneman Douglas high school.\"}, {\"start\": 79.74, \"end\": 87.34, \"text\": \"A scary situation in Bremerton, Washington was caught on camera.\"}, {\"start\": 87.34, \"end\": 94.28, \"text\": \"A woman was getting ready to leave her home when she noticed a man running down the street,\"}, {\"start\": 94.28, \"end\": 96.48, \"text\": \"heading towards her truck.\"}, {\"start\": 96.48, \"end\": 100.44, \"text\": \"Her child was inside the truck.\"}, {\"start\": 100.44, \"end\": 107.78, \"text\": \"When she walked to the passenger side, the man jumped in the driver's seat and try to\"}, {\"start\": 107.78, \"end\": 110.14, \"text\": \"steal the vehicle.\"}, {\"start\": 110.14, \"end\": 115.52, \"text\": \"The mother clung to the door, trying to stop him.\"}, {\"start\": 115.52, \"end\": 118.86, \"text\": \"She tried to pull him out but he slapped and hit her.\"}, {\"start\": 118.86, \"end\": 126.58, \"text\": \"Authorities say the man threatened to kill them as he tried to drive away, but he crashed\"}, {\"start\": 126.58, \"end\": 131.9, \"text\": \"into a concrete retaining wall with the woman clinging to the side of the truck.\"}, {\"start\": 131.9, \"end\": 133.56, \"text\": \"Take a look.\"}, {\"start\": 160.68, \"end\": 167.66, \"text\": \"The man eventually took off on foot but police caught up with him and arrested him.\"}, {\"start\": 170.02, \"end\": 187.8, \"text\": \"State Department spokesperson Heather Nauert issued a warning to college students thinking\"}, {\"start\": 187.8, \"end\": 198.8, \"text\": \"about going to Mexico on spring break, specifically Playa Del Carmen.\"}, {\"start\": 198.8, \"end\": 217.999, \"text\": \"Playa Del Carmen is a popular destination for US college students on spring break.\"}, {\"start\": 218.0, \"end\": 223.8, \"text\": \"Two weeks ago an explosive device went off on a tourist ferry, injuring several passengers.\"}, {\"start\": 223.8, \"end\": 229.62, \"text\": \"And last week another explosive device was found on a tourist ferry.\"}, {\"start\": 229.62, \"end\": 241.1, \"text\": \"The US consulate office in Playa Del Carmen is closed until further notice.\"}, {\"start\": 244.66, \"end\": 251.78, \"text\": \"If you've been thinking about a career in nursing, now is a great time to start preparing.\"}, {\"start\": 251.78, \"end\": 260.12, \"text\": \"America is facing a nursing shortage so hospitals are offering perks and incentives to attract\"}, {\"start\": 260.12, \"end\": 262.92, \"text\": \"qualified applicants.\"}, {\"start\": 262.92, \"end\": 273.16, \"text\": \"Some hospitals are offering five-figure signing bonuses and college tuition for employees\"}, {\"start\": 273.16, \"end\": 274.54, \"text\": \"and their children.\"}, {\"start\": 274.54, \"end\": 284.06, \"text\": \"Others are providing free housing and up to $20,000 in reimbursable relocation costs.\"}, {\"start\": 284.18, \"end\": 291.14, \"text\": \"The reason there is a shortage is because experienced nurses are retiring at a rapid rate.\"}, {\"start\": 291.2, \"end\": 298.82, \"text\": \"The American Nurses Association estimates the US will need more than 1 million new registered\"}, {\"start\": 298.82, \"end\": 302.72, \"text\": \"nurses in 2022.\"}, {\"start\": 305.74, \"end\": 312.3, \"text\": \"It appears Russia used a video game as part of its efforts to influence the 2016 presidential\"}, {\"start\": 312.3, \"end\": 315.14, \"text\": \"election.\"}, {\"start\": 315.2, \"end\": 329.54, \"text\": \"This is \\\"Hill-tendo\\\", an online game where players get Hillary Clinton to delete classified\"}, {\"start\": 329.54, \"end\": 336.28, \"text\": \"emails and collect money from foreign countries.\"}, {\"start\": 336.28, \"end\": 348.66, \"text\": \"\\\"Hill-tendo\\\" was created by Russians who wanted to make it go viral weeks before the election.\"}, {\"start\": 348.66, \"end\": 356.42, \"text\": \"But the game did not go viral as creators had hoped.\"}, {\"start\": 356.42, \"end\": 363.2, \"text\": \"One reason is because \\\"Hill-tendo\\\" could only be played on desktop and laptop computers,\"}, {\"start\": 363.2, \"end\": 366.08, \"text\": \"not smartphones.\"}, {\"start\": 368.2, \"end\": 383.02, \"text\": \"Two emperor penguins in Antarctica stumbled across a camera left in the ice by an expeditioner.\"}, {\"start\": 383.02, \"end\": 388.34, \"text\": \"The curious birds flipped it over to face skyward and then took a selfie video!\"}, {\"start\": 388.34, \"end\": 397.18, \"text\": \"The Australian Antarctic division posted this 38 second clip on its Twitter page.\"}, {\"start\": 397.18, \"end\": 398.92, \"text\": \"Here it is.\"}, {\"start\": 432.7, \"end\": 441.42, \"text\": \"The cute clip already has over 200,000 views and that number is going up!\"}, {\"start\": 443.26, \"end\": 446.62, \"text\": \"And those are your top stories for today.\"}, {\"start\": 446.62, \"end\": 448.04, \"text\": \"I'm Candace Jones.\"}, {\"start\": 448.04, \"end\": 450.62, \"text\": \"Thank you for watching Sign1News.\"}, {\"start\": 450.639, \"end\": 456.749, \"text\": \"Remember to like us on Facebook and follow us on Twitter.\"}, {\"start\": 456.749, \"end\": 464.24, \"text\": \"Sign1News. Your life. Your language.\"}]"
  },
  "fjhuFhu3vI0": {
    "video_id": "fjhuFhu3vI0",
    "title": "Univ. of Hawaii students panic after false missile alert (ASL - 1.14.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180115",
    "duration": 105,
    "view_count": 253,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 0.76, \"end\": 11.54, \"text\": \"Students at the University of Hawaii went into panic mode on Saturday after a false\"}, {\"start\": 11.54, \"end\": 13.98, \"text\": \"missile alert was issued.\"}, {\"start\": 13.98, \"end\": 21.0, \"text\": \"The alert went out on Saturday saying there was an inbound ballistic missile threat to\"}, {\"start\": 21.0, \"end\": 22.22, \"text\": \"the state.\"}, {\"start\": 22.22, \"end\": 34.5, \"text\": \"The message also told people to seek shelter right away and that it was not a drill.\"}, {\"start\": 34.5, \"end\": 46.84, \"text\": \"This is video of students running around campus in terror, scrambling for shelter.\"}, {\"start\": 46.84, \"end\": 53.32, \"text\": \"Some students could be heard yelling \\\"We gotta get out of here!\"}, {\"start\": 53.32, \"end\": 57.52, \"text\": \"We only have 15 minutes to get out of here!\\\"\"}, {\"start\": 57.52, \"end\": 72.46, \"text\": \"However Govenor David Ige says that was an error caused by someone pushing the wrong\"}, {\"start\": 72.46, \"end\": 81.98, \"text\": \"button during a shift change.\"}, {\"start\": 82.04, \"end\": 92.46, \"text\": \"The second alert that clarified the threat was not real was sent out 38 minutes later.\"}, {\"start\": 92.46, \"end\": 100.36, \"text\": \"Hawaii's emergency management administrator is working to find out what went wrong in\"}, {\"start\": 100.44, \"end\": 103.9, \"text\": \"the agency's operation center.\"}]"
  },
  "KtbsAj4epCk": {
    "video_id": "KtbsAj4epCk",
    "title": "NRA sues Florida (ASL - 3.10.18)",
    "channel": "Sign1News",
    "channel_id": "UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuyQHJ4y76-i0w9N33vT-kg",
    "upload_date": "20180310",
    "duration": 52,
    "view_count": 172,
    "description": "Sign1News is the first and only digital network, partnered with world news leader CNN, to offer on-line news and information in American Sign Language. Sign1News provides equal access to local, regional and national news and information to the Deaf and hard-of-hearing community via a daily post-produced broadcast. Sign1News: Your Life. Your Language.",
    "has_captions": true,
    "caption_languages": "ase",
    "caption_timestamps": "[{\"start\": 1.1, \"end\": 11.36, \"text\": \"The National Rifle Association isn't happy with the new gun laws.\"}, {\"start\": 11.36, \"end\": 21.52, \"text\": \"A few hours after the Florida gun law passed, the NRA filed a federal lawsuit to block it.\"}, {\"start\": 21.66, \"end\": 31.28, \"text\": \"The lawsuit argues the law violates the constitutional rights of Florida adults who have not yet\"}, {\"start\": 31.28, \"end\": 34.5, \"text\": \"turned 21.\"}, {\"start\": 34.5, \"end\": 49.32, \"text\": \"Officials with the NRA said the bill punishes law abiding gun owners for the criminal acts\"}, {\"start\": 49.32, \"end\": 51.88, \"text\": \"of one deranged individual.\"}]"
  },
  "3SaL_1cqzAE": {
    "video_id": "3SaL_1cqzAE",
